502031.detail: Big sister and I got lost on on this strange island and saw some weird stuff... What was weird about it? Look, it was really weird, that's all!
502031.touch: D-don't stare at me like that... Fine, I'll give you a third of my ice cream... Ugh, okay, half! But no more than that!
502031.login: B-big sister, where are we...? And where is everyone...? Eek! I-I think I just heard something... Oh, right, this place is uninhabited.
502031.battle: Will you give me food if we win this? Pretty please?
502031.main: Liquor chocolates? Wait, no, big sister! You shouldn't eat those...!|Big sister told me the dining table is a battlefield of its own, so I'm gonna stay on my guard!|Aww... I wanna ride on the Commander's shoulders too...
502031.upgrade: Fried noodles! Grilled fish! Ice cream!
502031.unlock: Shaved ice is better than steamed buns, fireworks are prettier than shaved ice, and more precious than fireworks is...
502031.drop_descrip: Shaved ice is better than steamed buns, fireworks are prettier than shaved ice, and more precious than fireworks is...
502031.win_mvp: Hey Commander, I wanna have croquettes today!

306080.detail: Chiyoda and I are partners in carrying out shrine duties. Even though Chiyoda can be pretty annoying at times, there are still times she's fun to be around.
306080.touch: Who?! ... Oh, it's you. I thought it was a prank from that pink-haired Union girl.
306080.login: Oh, you're here. There's some red bean jelly from Chiyoda on your desk. Feel free to take some.
306080.battle: I have to make sure to be careful...
306080.hp_warning: This is bad... I hope Chiyoda... is alright...
306080.feeling2: The one thing I hope I never have to see again is the formation of a "decoy fleet"...
306080.headtouch: Do you like touching my bangs like Chiyoda does?
306080.mission_complete: The mission is... complete. That's good.
306080.main: Isuzu... is quite a scaredy cat, but she's a good girl. But even that side of her is cute.|Chiyoda always insists on doing my hair this way, so I let her. However, I always feel a bit apologetic for making her do so much...|I'm at least confident in my Kagura dancing skills. If you get the chance, please come and watch.
306080.feeling5: Commander, won't you rely on me some more? I'm actually pretty good at spoiling people, you know... Oh I know... would you like me to give you a lap pillow, or something...?
306080.upgrade: For the time being, thanks, Commander.
306080.unlock: I am Chitose, light carrier of the Sakura Empire. Commander, I look forward to receiving your guidance. By the way, is it true that Chiyoda is also here? ...Don't worry, I was merely inquiring.
306080.feeling4: Cooking, cleaning, even taking care of my things... Chiyoda takes care of it all. ... Basically, it's not that I can't do these tasks. If I put my mind to it, I can do it... I totally can...
306080.feeling1: Commander. Get away from Chiyoda. As far as you possibly can.
306080.propose: If that's how you feel about me, I'll gladly accept your feelings... I'll pray for your safety every day, and be your refuge from your daily hardships. I hope... you'll come look for me whenever you're feeling troubled, because I want to pamper you like I do with Chiyoda...
306080.profile: Though Chiyoda and I were originally designed as seaplane tenders, during a certain war, we were remodeled into aircraft carriers. Whether it's due to my lack of skill or my inability to oppose the passing of time... I wasn't able to be of much use until the end.
306080.mission: Here are some more missions. Isn't it bad to let them pile up like this?
306080.home: I'm glad you're safe... I made a protective charm for you, and also one for Chiyoda. Please keep it safely inside your clothes.
306080.win_mvp: I'm glad... that I was able to be a help to everyone else.
306080.expedition: The commission team has returned safely. What a relief.
couple_encourage: Alright, alright... We'll go together.
D-Don't call out to me so endearingly...
I'm here. There's nothing to fear.
306080.mail: There's a letter addressed to you. Please check it out.
306080.feeling3: I don't dislike having to pamper Chiyoda... If anything, I might actually find it quite endearing...
306080.lose: We're pulling back. Chiyoda, please be safe...

301171.touch: A cannonball this is not, it is a will-o'-wisp!
301171.main: Commander, come, let us go trick or treating!|I'm working hard so that my sisters may eat the most delicious pumpkin around!|Commander, surely tonight you will forgive any tricks played on you?
301171.unlock: Commander, trick or treat! I expect you to give some candy to my sisters as well! These will-o'-wisps? Hahaha~ I tried imitating that gloomy sister of mine!
301171.drop_descrip: Commander, trick or treat! I expect you to give some candy to my sisters as well! These will-o'-wisps? Hahaha~ I tried imitating that gloomy sister of mine!
301171.touch2: I will cover my smokestack with this pumpkin, then... Ooh! Smoke is coming out of the pumpkin! Wait, what is that smell... Oh no! I burned the pumpkin!

302110.detail: My... horn? If it makes people remember me, then I believe it's not all that bad.
302110.touch: I'm standing by. Please give me your orders.
302110.login: Welcome back. Let's try to get a lot of work done today.
302110.hp_warning: Don't panic! We still have a chance!
302110.feeling2: Pardon me, Commander, I'm occupied with the task you gave me... Okay, how may I help? Communication? Yes, of course, communication is important.
302110.mission_complete: I have completed my inspection of the mission rewards, Commander.
302110.main: My sister is... probably sitting somewhere, alone, lamenting the past again. Commander, would you please excuse me for a moment?|A secretary should be the Commander's right hand. Please don't hesitate to give me orders.|I was the first heavy cruiser to sink in the war... Oh, never mind, it was nothing important.
302110.feeling5: Jealousy... you say? It's never been on my mind... As long as I have my dear sister and my dear Commander... everything will probably be okay... I think?
302110.upgrade: Your kindness is highly appreciated. I swear to repay it one day.
302110.unlock: My name is Mikuma. I'm Mogami's little sister. If... if you don't mind, could you please look after her? She has a bit of an unusual personality, you see...
302110.feeling4: I'm always willing to support my sister, but owing to her somber personality... I don't think anyone but you can truly guide her, Commander...
302110.feeling1: I've gotta warn my sister about how untrustworthy you are...
302110.propose: Sorry for taking so long, Commander. Huh? I should call you "darling"? Umm... D-darling... This feels a little awkward, but it's something I should slowly get used to. Now, I hope we will be together for many long years.
302110.drop_descrip: Mogami-class heavy cruiser number two – Mikuma.
302110.profile: I am Mikuma, the second ship of the Mogami-class. I collided with my sister in Midway, but I don't resent her for it. On the contrary: she... Ah, forgive me for changing the topic so suddenly... I shall do everything I can for the fleet, so please give me your orders.
302110.touch2: ... Commander, please be wary of accidental discharges from my cannons.
302110.mission: I have organized the mission rewards, Commander. Could you confirm them, please?
302110.win_mvp: This is nothing to get thrilled about!
302110.expedition: A commission has finished, Commander. If you're occupied at the moment, please send me in your stead.
couple_encourage: Mogami, try not to stray too far from me.
302110.mail: Here is the letter that arrived today, Commander.
302110.feeling3: All Mogami-class cruisers were part of Cruiser Division 7, but because Kumano and Suzuya were launched later than me, it was I who had to look after Mogami. And for that reason, they aren't as close to her as I am.
302110.lose: *Gah*...! This will serve as a lesson...!

102200.detail: I eat so much every day, but I'm not growing at all... Why...?
102200.touch: It's important to keep your energy up, Commander! Here, have a chocolate bar!
102200.login: Morning, Commander! How about a chocolate bar?
102200.battle: I'll take you all on! I ain't scared!
102200.feeling2: Hey, Commander, me and some of the girls are forming a Port Explorers' Team! You wanna come with us?
102200.mission_complete: Hey, the rewards are here! I got lots of tasty snacks to trade. Whaddya say, Commander?
102200.main: I've got lots of little sisters, and I love each and every one of 'em! Lemme introduce you someday!|Hey, Commander, is there a blue-haired girl in the fleet, about yea big, always staring at herself in the mirror? You mind if I go play with her?|Being this small is kind of inconvenient sometimes. ... Like when? Like when I'm trying to help somebody with something...?
102200.feeling5: Heh... I was right to ask you, Commander! You always help me out. That's why I love you! From now on, I'm gonna come to you anytime I don't understand something. Sound good?
102200.unlock: Hello, my name is Cleveland! My dream is to one day join the Solomon Knights! I'm working hard towards that goal every day!
102200.feeling4: C-Commander, lemme ask you something. Helena said if I eat too much chocolate, I'll get fat and you won't wanna be with me anymore ... Is... is that true?
102200.feeling1: Everybody's waiting for me! See ya, Commander!
102200.propose: This means we're best friends forever? I'll take good care of it! Hehee, if you ever get into trouble, Commander, just let me know. I'll take good care of you!
102200.profile: I'm the big sister of the Cleveland-class... but I guess that's obvious from my name alone. I may be a light cruiser, but I can match a heavy cruiser no problem! I am gonna dominate the seas, after all!
102200.touch2: Huh? You wanna rub my belly?
102200.mission: Commander, go bang out that mission!
102200.home: Need a little pick-me-up, Commander? I got all kinds of snacks on me!
102200.expedition: Race you to the pier, Commander! Winner gets a prize!
couple_encourage: I'm Cleveland! Let's play!
102200.mail: New mail's here. Hey, you're as popular as me, Commander!
102200.feeling3: I know how busy you are, Commander, and you still make time to come along with us... All right, from this day forward, I'm making the Commander an honorary member of our Explorers' Team!
102200.lose: Commander, this is looking kinda bad...?

207040.detail: In both love and war, one should be brave~ So, be brave, and if you need support, I shall be there!
207040.touch: When you feel down, I also do. Come on, you have someone as beautiful as me beside you, so why not be happy?
207040.login: The quiet sea, the cool sea breeze... Even in this moment, the birth of new, beautiful things blesses us.
207040.battle: Sigh, all that cannons and gunpowder can do is make is war even uglier...
207040.hp_warning: Oh dear, I've let my guard down.
207040.feeling2: You know about me from the Battle of Trafalgar? Umm, aren't you thinking of somebody else? Please, Commander~ Who you're thinking of is totally unrelated to me.
207040.mission_complete: Fine, but just this one time! I won't help you with your missions a second time!
207040.main: War is ugly. And this olive wreath is the symbol of peace and beauty.|Tirpitz, if you won't come out and have fun with me then I'll bomb your room again!|I don't like violence, but using it is often the quickest solution to many problems...
207040.feeling5: I wonder what the future you will be like, Commander~ Of course, I already quite like the way you are right now. ...Goodness, you're blushing ear to ear. How utterly adorable you are~
207040.upgrade: Words are not needed to praise me! It's not people's words that touch the heart, it's their actions!
207040.unlock: I am the one called Victorious, Aircraft Carrier of the Royal Navy. Yes, sing my name as you herald the coming of the symbol of victory. As long as I am here, our endeavours shall be smooth!
207040.feeling4: I'm not in such a great mood... Are you free, Commander? Great! Then let me dress you in something fabulous! Seeing beautiful things makes me feel better, you see!
207040.feeling1: I'm fed up~! I'll knock you out stone cold!
207040.propose: Don't think too hard about it. Just follow my lead at your own pace. ...Come on, this is a day to celebrate, don't be so nervous~ From this day on, you'd better work hard to always please me!
207040.skill: O beautiful world, sing to me a song!
207040.profile: I'm Victorious, Illustrious-class aircraft carrier number two! From the Atlantic Ocean to the Indian Ocean, and even the Pacific... where the ocean breeze goes, I follow!
207040.touch2: Y-you just did "that," didn't you?! B-by "that," I mean...
207040.mission: Only I have the privilege of being selfish. Don't even think about pushing missions onto me.
207040.home: To celebrate your victory, why not wear this olive wreath? I'm certain it'll suit you.
207040.win_mvp: When my foes have been this thoroughly defeated... not even I, the symbol of victory, can truly be glad.
207040.expedition: Stop loafing around! I promised the commission team that I'd use my planes to photograph the moment they entered the port!
couple_encourage: Pleasure to meet again, little Ms. Flat-As-A-Pancake.
Illustrious, y-your bust is just too busty!
Let's bring your sister along for a tea party next time.
Can you talk like normal people?
207040.mail: Handwritten letters are so much better than typed ones. Don't you think it's interesting how you can deduce the author's emotions based on their handwriting, Commander?
207040.feeling3: My part in the pursuit of Bismarck and Operation Tungsten? I was just in the mood to help, I wasn't at all trying to earn any honours.
207040.lose: Remaining dignified even in defeat: this is how one should lose a battle!

502030.detail: What are you looking at, Commander?
502030.touch: Commander, do you also want a hug? I hug my big sister all the time.
502030.login: Commander, have you eaten yet? You can’t work on an empty stomach.
502030.battle: Do I get any tasty food for winning?
502030.feeling2: Big sister always says that we are too poor to have food in the pot, but every time I open the lid, there’s always food in there! What’s the deal with that?
502030.mission_complete: So many rewards, Commander! Can we trade them for buns?
502030.main: Socks? Big sister said we should spend less money, so we share one pair together...|Kung Fu? Big sister said we could earn some Coins by performing on the street, so I learned that too...|Pandas? On our heads? They're also sisters!
502030.feeling5: I will be satisfied as long as I can be with Commander all the time, and just see my sister every now and then. Hmm? Big Sister would cry? Why?
502030.unlock: Commander? Big sister told me that commanders who can’t even put food on the table are no good. Can you support yourself? ...Then, how about me?
502030.feeling4: Big sister told me that finding someone who can feed me is more important than finding someone I like. Since I like Commander and get plenty of food, there shouldn’t be any problems.
502030.feeling1: Commander... are you one of those "bad guys" that big sister talks about?
502030.propose: Does this mean that I should only listen to Commander from now on instead of my big sister? ...Make my own decision? Hm... then, I shall listen to both of you.
502030.drop_descrip: Ning Hai-class Light Cruser, Ping Hai
502030.profile: I'm Ning Hai, the first ship of the Ning Hai-class. Big sister told me to say this when I was introducing myself. Ah? I'm Ping Hai? That's right! Then... I'm Ping Hai, the first ship of the Ning Hai-class... I'm wrong again? This is so confusing...
502030.touch2: Big sister told me to beat up any bad guys that I come across. But what is a bad guy?
502030.mission: Big sister says that missions won’t complete themselves if I’m daydreaming. Does that mean they will if I practice kung fu?
502030.home: Whenever big sister is tired, the only way to make her happy is by giving her steamed buns. Do you want some, Commander?
502030.win_mvp: Number one? Does that taste good?
502030.expedition: Commander, Commander! Big sister said that I have to tell you whenever a commission is finished.
couple_encourage: Big sister! Do you want some buns?
502030.mail: Big sister says that checking the mail in a timely manner is a common courtesy! Commander, want to read these?
502030.feeling3: Big sister said I shouldn’t be alone with Commander... is it because she wants the buns all for herself? Then, I shall come visit Commander more often from now on!

902012.detail: I dig the design of this Dragon Empery outfit. Uh, that's NOT an invitation for you to ogle me all you want, okay?
902012.touch: What's up? You thinkin' about finally introducing me to your family?
902012.login: You're leaving me out in the dust here, Commander! I'll die from sheer boredom if you won't hang out with me!
902012.main: Got any red envelopes for me, Commander? Talk about lame, there's just money inside... I expected something that's like, more novel, and now I'm disappointed!|Get together with the extended family over New Year's, hang up fai chun decorations, aaand... what's left? Courtesy calls? Take me along, Commander! I won't embarrass you, pinky promise!|I know! Let's meet up and do festive stuff with Dunkerque!
902012.unlock: Happy New Year, again! So, you wanna try sharing this "cross-cupped wine?" What, it's not a drinking game? Welp, I guess I've still got a whole ton to learn about the Dragon Empery's customs~
902012.drop_descrip: Happy New Year, again! So, you wanna try sharing this "cross-cupped wine?" What, it's not a drinking game? Welp, I guess I've still got a whole ton to learn about the Dragon Empery's customs~
902012.touch2: Watch it, or you'll make it come off!
902012.home: You can feel the festival spirit everywhere you look! Isn't that nice?

401233.detail: Ugh... how am I supposed to keep smiling all day long? My jaw's gone stiff already...
401233.touch: Commander, you can't just chat with me while I'm on duty. I've got work to do.
401233.main: Commander, it's not polite to stare... oh! Smiling, I'm smiling... *cough cough*! What can I get for you?|So if you order this set, you can choose from one of these, or these. Not a bad deal, eh?|Hmm... I should really take this opportunity to learn some new recipes. Oh, sorry, this is your menu~
401233.feeling5: *Sigh* Being a waitress is a brutal job... but, there are some upsides. Hehe, Commander, what do you think...? Does my smile look a bit more natural now?
401233.unlock: Welcome! A table for one today? Um... Commander, my smile doesn’t look stiff... right?
401233.drop_descrip: Welcome! A table for one today? Um... Commander, my smile doesn’t look stiff... right?
401233.touch2: Commander, if you get in my way again I'll have to ask you to leave!
401233.home: Please, have a look at today's specials, Commander.

408090.detail: Yeah, what? You fancy how a U-boat in her off time looks?
408090.login: Look who's early. Here I was hoping to see you panicking over being late.
408090.hp_warning: Should probably retreat while I still can, I guess!
408090.feeling2: During most my missions I'm honestly just bored out of my mind and pray I find somethin' worth my time. If you ever feel bored, go hit up some of the U-boats at port.
408090.mission_complete: So, what is it? Need someone to fetch ya those rewards?
408090.main: It's not the foes you can see that you should fear, it's the ones you can't see. Like us U-boats, for instance...|Step one: dive. Step two: wait. While we U-boats can hold our breaths for ages, sometimes I just like goin' for a leisurely swim.|"The Oak-Leaves Patrol"... Heheh, that's got a nice ring to it. Still, all we really did was make a pack and go huntin' for targets.
408090.feeling5: Someday I wanna take you with me on a trip across the sea, just the two of us. We could write a journal as we go and make a book or even movie out of it... Actually, that'd be weird, so let's not. But as long as we make some fond memories, I'm happy.
408090.upgrade: Oh man, I can't wait for the next sortie.
408090.unlock: Sup. I'm U-96, Type VIIC U-boat and member of the famous Vorwärts wolfpack. Hehe, I'll have you drowning in reports of my success soon enough.
408090.feeling4: You can get onto my rigging while I'm surfaced, can'tcha? Don't worry, I ain't gonna just dump ya in the middle of the ocean. So, how's that sound? Wanna ride with me?
408090.feeling1: You know where you belong? In a shark's stomach. Meh, whatever.
408090.propose: You got me, I'll give ya that much... But I've still got the chance to strike back. Close your eyes! ...Mwah! Heheh, hit ya right in the heart with that one, didn't I?
408090.drop_descrip: Iron Blood Type VIIC submarine – U-96.
408090.profile: The name's U-96, Iron Blood Type VIIC U-boat, part of the 7th U-boat Flotilla. I made some real juicy contributions over my 11 patrols in the war. Never did fare well against aircraft, though... But don't let that worry ya, Commander. I'm still an ace, and I ain't never gonna let ya down.
408090.touch2: What? You seriously like touching me here?
408090.mission: What's this? Still got unfinished missions, do we?
408090.home: Lemme see that map, Commander... All right, cool... 'Kay, so the spot I marked would be perfect for an ambush next sortie. If ya need it done, just hit me up.
408090.win_mvp: Now do ya see what an ace is capable of?
408090.expedition: The commission team's back. Good thing those sheep didn't get eaten by wolves, eh.
couple_encourage: There ain't no escaping the wolfpack!
408090.mail: That mailbox is gonna get full sooner or later. And don't say I didn't warn ya.
408090.feeling3: If ya think U-boat combat is that fascinating, you could always come with me on the next sortie. Oh wait, you can't stay underwater all that long, can ya? Then how's about I teach you how to dive like a pro?
408090.lose: Whatever. Next time's gonna be much better.

103061.touch: You think Indy's suuuuper cute too, right? She really is! If you want, I'll let you cuddle with my Indy plushie just a bit!
103061.login: Oh, Commander, have you seen Indy? I want to dress her in some super adorable clothes I made~ Guhehehe~
103061.main: Commander, why don't we go for lunch? Of course, my dear Indy will be there too!|Whether on the way to school, in class, or heading home, I'm always with Indy... School life is the best thing EVER!|I bet you'd make a good teacher, Commander... So, please, take pictures of Indy from every angle during class! Later, I'll trade you for regular pictures of her!
103061.unlock: Commander, look, look! This is my handmade Indy plushie! Isn't it utterly adorable?! It's the magnum opus of my work in the Arts & Crafts Club!
103061.drop_descrip: Commander, look, look! This is my handmade Indy plushie! Isn't it utterly adorable?! It's the magnum opus of my work in the Arts & Crafts Club!
103061.touch2: Eek?! Be careful, Commander! I nearly pricked myself with my needle!
103061.home: When Indy's dyed rose red from the setting sun on the way back from school... ahhh, she's so cuuuuuute! Don't you want to see how she looks too, Commander?!

308060.detail: You want something from me, don't you? ... Well, even if you don't...
308060.touch: Don't touch me for no reason! ... It's a massage? O-okay... Continue...
308060.login: You're very late! ... A submarine such as myself is extremely patient, but that doesn't mean you can keep me waiting for this long...
308060.battle: Let's go! We're hunting big game!
308060.feeling2: Hmph! Doubt me all you want, but I'm THE Sakura Empire submarine that sank an important carrier. Now, get on your knees and worship me.
308060.mission_complete: You've done well! Here's your reward.
308060.main: I'm bored... Entertain me, Commander!|I'm tired... I like it better in the ocean...|Hammann? If she wants to berate me then she can go ahead and try! I'll turn the tables on her!
308060.feeling5: Hmph! If you prefer girls who are honest about their feelings, why not hook up with someone more honest than me? ... WHAT?! Hammann is NOT more honest with her feelings than me!
308060.upgrade: All right! I've become even stronger!
308060.unlock: I'm I-168, but do call me Iroha. I expect you to know how to handle an extraordinary and decorated vessel such as myself!
308060.feeling4: Ever since I sank Yorktown in the war, I've been getting occasional angry glances from Hammann... B-but aren't we all friends now? I mean hey, even Yorktown herself says she's let go of it!
308060.feeling1: I hate scum like you. Don't come near me ever again.
308060.propose: F-finally you decided to open up to me... You did right to choose me... Ehehe... W-what's that mean?! YOU'RE the one not being honest here!
308060.profile: I am the submarine I-168. In the war, I avenged Hiryuu by taking out Yorktown and Hammann. Besides that... well... I really tried... but wasn't able to sink any other ships...
308060.mission: A mission...? Hmph! I'll show you how it's done! Now listen veeery carefully♪
308060.home: Nicely done. Now sit down and relax.
308060.win_mvp: I DID IT! You see that? Did you see it?!
308060.expedition: Marvelous work, everybody! ... Wonder if they found any rare stuff...
couple_encourage: Hammann, we're all friends now, you know!
308060.mail: A letter for you. Do check it later! ... I wonder if there are any for me...
308060.feeling3: Tooru! I told you to quit tickling me with your Type A! ... Wait a sec, you're not Tooru!

502033.detail: I think big sister really likes her idol outfit.
502033.touch: Commander, you want to get up on stage with me?
502033.login: Commander, are you here for my show?
502033.mission_complete: They gave me so much good stuff to eat. I love it!
502033.main: Big sister says all I need to do is be myself up on stage, but the truth is I don't know how to be myself unless she tells me...|Commander, do you think I should try doing kung fu up on stage? Like this.. hiyaa!|I think everybody really likes Baobao. Let me do a show with Baobao next time!
502033.feeling5: Being an idol with my big sister is so much fun. And it's been a really long time since I've seen her so happy... but I'd be even happier with you, Commander.
502033.unlock: Big sister says that even though we have some money now, we still have to save as much as we can. Um... Anyway, I'm the younger "Dragon Sister," Ping Hai. Erm... I'm kind of hungry. Do you maybe have something to eat?
502033.drop_descrip: Big sister says that even though we have some money now, we still have to save as much as we can. Um... Anyway, I'm the younger "Dragon Sister," Ping Hai. Erm... I'm kind of hungry. Do you maybe have something to eat?
502033.touch2: I think I'm wearing it right?
502033.mission: Big sister says more offers means more money...
502033.expedition: Commander, can I go with you to welcome everyone home?
502033.mail: Commander, can you help me reply to all this fan mail? I can't do it all by myself...
502033.lose: Big sister, my clothes ripped... sew them for me...

103131.detail: I've been paying attention in class! See, here are the notes I took.
103131.touch: Do you want to have some fries? I’ll share with you a little.
103131.login: Good morning Commander. Well, just wait for me to finish my burger and I’ll get started on today’s mission.
103131.main: Coke, burgers and fries—— Yes, let’s get that for lunch today |Smartphone? Yes, Quincy gave this to me, although it doesn’t really work well… |Class is so boring, but its not good to skip... hmmm——
103131.feeling5: Do you want to play with me after class, Commander? Em… I don’t have any particular place in mind, I just want to play with you, that’s all.
103131.unlock: Textbooks, pencils and erasers... hey, must students always pay attention in class... Commander? Can you arrange for us to get more extracurricular activities?
103131.drop_descrip: Textbooks, pencils and erasers... hey, must students always pay attention in class... Commander? Can you arrange for us to get more extracurricular activities?
103131.touch2: Th-this is against the school policy!
103131.home: Finally, class is over! Where shall we go...

902011.detail: I'll throw the swim ring at you if you get close to drowning. Relax, knowin' you, I'm sure you'll catch it!
902011.touch: Whoa there, trying to startle me? Sadly for you, I saw that coming from miles away~
902011.login: I'm not gonna swim all day, so I'll just skip the warm-ups. Should be no biggie!
902011.main: We don't really NEED to swim just 'cause we've got a pool, do we? Nothing wrong with just dipping our toes, you know.|Over here, Commander! Ka-splash! Ahahahah! Feelin' refreshed now?|Hmm... Feels a little weird, not having my hands full with something...
902011.unlock: Summertime means pool time! Oh, hey, Commander. What are you waiting for? Come over and let's have fun!
902011.drop_descrip: Summertime means pool time! Oh, hey, Commander. What are you waiting for? Come over and let's have fun!
902011.touch2: Ahahah. So you wanna practice holding your breath, is that it, Commander?
902011.home: Could you throw me that ball, Commander? Merci~

502032.touch: Happy Mid-Autumn Festival! Do you wanna make a traditional lantern, Commander?
502032.main: Om nom... Hey, Commander, what flavor of mooncake do you like?|Just so you know, Commander, I'm an unrivaled champion at hammering mooncake!|The sweet osmanthus cakes my sister made smell delicious. You want one, Commander?
502032.unlock: Commander, happy Mid-Autumn Festival! I have mooncakes, pomegranates, and osmanthus cakes... Mm... This holiday is the best!
502032.drop_descrip: Commander, happy Mid-Autumn Festival! I have mooncakes, pomegranates, and osmanthus cakes... Mm... This holiday is the best!
502032.touch2: I feel like I could hop all the way up to the moon in this outfit...

107291.detail: It's a little embarrassing, but I do always sleep with this little one here...
107291.touch: These are my favorite pajamas... They aren't too childish? ... They suit me? Ahahaha... Th-thanks...
107291.login: Good morning... Sorry, Commander, do you mind if I wash my face first...?
107291.main: Good sleep is very important to your work. Commander, do make sure you're getting enough rest.|Sorry, Commander, I'm fading again... Zzz...|A pajama party...? I want to go... I wonder if Independence would be interested...
107291.feeling5: Whether I'm hard at work or resting comfortably, you're always here, Commander... And I wouldn't trade it for the world. Hehe. Commander, would you like to hold the little one?
107291.unlock: Yaaaaawn... Huh!? Commander!? You scared me... I was just going to lie down and... Um, yes, with little Hellcat here... Goodnight...
107291.drop_descrip: Yaaaaawn... Huh!? Commander!? You scared me... I was just going to lie down and... Um, yes, with little Hellcat here... Goodnight...
107291.home: Welcome back, Commander... Why don't you take a rest? I can lend you my pillow...

905012.detail: You wanna go lookin' for treasure? There's no damn treasure 'round here. But one day... Hmph, one day, when we've achieved a boring peace, I'll give you a taste of what a real treasure hunt is like.
905012.touch: Ack! Don't put your damn ice-cold soda on me! You're on thin ice, buddy...
905012.login: Don't you go touchin' my stuff without permission! I'll knock ya out cold.
905012.main: Sorry, but this hammock's only big enough for one of us. Ya wanna relax, get your own. I ain't your personal servant.|Just how much damn work do you have if you're even bringin' it up here...? You just like being with me...? Tsk...|Wha–? Is... Is that Surcouf? The hell... How'd she end up dozing off in here? That girl's a real piece of work.
905012.feeling5: Man... The sun's crazy bright out today... What, you're still here? How long are ya gonna hang around? Hmph, you're real good, both at making me happy AND making me mad, you know that?
905012.unlock: You damn scalawag... You don't just sneak into someone's hideaway without consequences, ya know. Though, I found this place by pure chance too. Don't go tellin' anyone else about it!
905012.drop_descrip: You damn scalawag... You don't just sneak into someone's hideaway without consequences, ya know. Though, I found this place by pure chance too. Don't go tellin' anyone else about it!
905012.touch2: You're not the only one who can do whatever ya want just 'cause nobody else will come here. I can, too. Understand?
905012.home: Would you stop comin' here right after returning to port? Don't want people catching wind of this place and turning it into a playground.

905013.detail: Aid with getting dressed? This is nothing compared to a ceremonial Iris dress. Not to mention it suits me better. Don't ya agree?
905013.touch: What, you wanna see me brandish one of these?
905013.login: Work, same as always, huh? Tell me if there's anything I oughta know.
905013.main: Sakura Empire-style badminton? Sounds fun. I'll knock that shuttlecock beyond the horizon!|I hate it when people approach me to either give or get a hug. Never asked for their damn compassion.|Wagashi, for me? Thanks. Dunkerque sure is considerate as always.
905013.feeling5: Not to say I've grown soft, but I have gotten too used to you bein' around. I don't mind it – hell, I like it. I'm all but dependent on you, that's just how important you are to me.
905013.unlock: Bonne année... Or rather, I should say "Happy New Year" here, yes? A year of peace and prosperity passes, and we are here to welcome another... and I must thank you for making that possible.
905013.drop_descrip: Bonne année... Or rather, I should say "Happy New Year" here, yes? A year of peace and prosperity passes, and we are here to welcome another... and I must thank you for making that possible.
905013.home: You're back? Seems you've got girls queuein' up to meet you. Me, not so much...
905013.win_mvp: I'm not the type to underestimate anyone.

502026.detail: I never knew pandas are omnivores. I'd always thought they only ate bamboo...
502026.touch: A baozi? You're not supposed to feed pandas with stuff you'd feed Ping! ...It's for me? In that case, th-thanks...
502026.login: Commander! Good timing! Could you go get some bamboo?
502026.main: Have some bamboo too, Da Bao. Eat it slowly now, so you don't choke!|These cubs might not look all that heavy, but they weigh a lot for their size.|You can't just play all day, Ping! There are charity missions to do, don't forget that! Same for you, Commander!
502026.unlock: Good boy. Chew thoroughly before you swallow. I never thought I'd help with a charity event for nature, but Da Bao's made a lot of new friends because of it. Keep up the good work, Commander and Ping!
502026.drop_descrip: Good boy. Chew thoroughly before you swallow. I never thought I'd help with a charity event for nature, but Da Bao's made a lot of new friends because of it. Keep up the good work, Commander and Ping!
502026.home: The mommy panda is pretty wary of letting people near her babies... What would her caretakers do in this situation?

301610.detail: This time too... I swear to protect my friends!
301610.touch: Hm? What are you looking at, Commander?
301610.login: Now's not the time to lose focus, Commander.
301610.battle: This wind... is perfect for battle!
301610.feeling2: Commander, history surely won't repeat itself... right?
301610.mission_complete: Your grades are going up, Commander.
301610.main: Tanikaze, until you finish your training, don't expect to get much beauty sleep!|Though I may be but a single destroyer, I'll still do all I can to protect everyone.|Bou-no-misaki... where it all came to an end...|
301610.feeling5: For as long as the wind blows, I will always be by your side.
301610.unlock: Hamakaze, 13th ship of the Kagerou-class destroyers, reporting for duty. Commander, try not to get my name wrong.
301610.feeling4: The breeze feels really nice today... But we can't afford to rest yet! Yamato... wait for me...
301610.propose: M-maybe we should wait until it's all over... Th-that said, I'd feel bad if I rejected you now, so I'll have to accept it... Hey, stop laughing!
301610.profile: I'm Hamakaze, 13th Kagerou-class destroyer. Although I took part in quite a few battles, it feels like I spent more time rescuing friends than sinking foes... And now, I fight once more to protect my friends.
301610.touch2: Eek! ... Commander, just where do you think you're touching?
301610.home: Great job. Did everyone do their job during the sortie?
301610.win_mvp: Heheh! This is nothing spectacular for me!
301610.expedition: Well done... Commissions are hardly a big deal compared to Rat Transports, right?
301610.mail: Reading through these reports should be your top priority.
301610.feeling3: I hope one day... Destroyer Division 17 can reunite here...
301610.lose: I have to rescue the survivors...

699010.detail: I don't mind you acting as my own Rustichello. In fact, I adore having someone who chronicles my life. Oh, but please do omit my mistakes!
699010.touch: For what have I been summoned?
699010.login: So you've come prepared to sacrifice a portion of your time on this mortal coil in the name of productivity? Magnificent!
699010.battle: Soldiers, weigh anchor! For the glory of Sardegna!
699010.hp_warning: Danger is an opportunity! Have at you!
699010.feeling2: Oh? You're approaching me? Instead of keeping me at arm's length, you wish to get to know me? Then by all means... Hehehe!
699010.mission_complete: You've finished those chores? Magnificent! Now we can focus on more important matters.
699010.main: All things of value are bound to fall into someone's hands, sooner or later. Better it be yours than someone else's.|The golden Dragon Empery... I have countless stories of it to share if you'll only lend me an ear!|Looking at the map... This port is unbelievably small. Has the thought of expanding it never crossed your mind?
699010.feeling5: You! What is the deal with you? I never said you should "spread the glory of Marco Polo's name!" You... You... You're too ambitious for your own good!
699010.upgrade: The greater one's strength, the more privileges one is entitled to. You know this, yes? Magnificent!
699010.unlock: I hope you know what you're in for, now that you've awoken me. Hehehe... You look to be a commander of valor and culture. Magnificent! I am Marco Polo. Now, come! Our first order of business is to spread the Sardegna Empire's glory through the world!
699010.feeling4: You command a whole fleet of ships, and you don't even try to use them to spread the Empire's– I mean, your own glory? It truly baffles me.
699010.feeling1: If not for your position, I would've sent you away to... Never you mind. Hmph!
699010.propose: A woman with great aspirations doesn't let commitments bind her. But... for you, I'll make an exception. And don't you dare vanish on me until your ambitions are realized!
699010.profile: I am Marco Polo, Sardegnian battleship. Compare me with Veneto if you so wish, but just for the record: I could do her job much better. Ohohoho!
699010.mission: New missions? Be magnificent and get them done in a jiffy, okay? Chop-chop.
699010.home: I believe the secretary should have the power to issue commands. Only while you're away, of course.
699010.win_mvp: They're surrendering already? So... We won? What pathetic adversaries we have.
699010.expedition: The commission team has returned. Take it from me, you really ought to venture out with them to see the sights of the world more often.
couple_encourage: A leader who second-guesses herself is no leader at all.
For the glory of the Empire!
699010.mail: A letter of surrender from our enemies? Then allow me to establish our terms.
699010.feeling3: You possess insight and views superior to those of commonplace boors. But, as it stands, you could use some more... well, ambition.
699010.lose: You wretches... I will inflict this humiliation back at you a hundred times over!

101410.detail: What are you staring at? I'm not going to transform...
101410.touch: Self-defense mode activating... Bahaha, you should've seen your face!
101410.login: Stanly has entered work mode! By the way, it doesn't last very long.
101410.feeling2: Stanly's in happy mode today – I can take on any task with a spring in my step!
101410.mission_complete: Whoa! The rewards are here! Commander, let's go take a look!
101410.main: Commander, join me in becoming a hero of justice... Bahaha! Just kidding! |Commander, are you still in work mode? Jeez, don't keep me waiting much longer... |Commander, your hair sure is funny! Let's give it a good twirl~!
101410.feeling5: Warning, Stanly has entered the "will self-destruct if not within a 3-meter radius of Commander" mode... I-I'm serious! So, I'm going to make sure I'm never separated from you, heehee~
101410.upgrade: Strengthening complete! I'm gonna reward myself to a little rest and relaxation!
101410.unlock: Good morning, Commander. I'm Stanly, a destroyer from the Eagle Union. I will follow your every order to bring you victory... Pffft! Bahaha! S-Sorry, this whole "serious introduction" thing totally cramps my style, haha!
101410.feeling4: As long as I'm with you, my happiness gauge will continue to fill up! So, Commander, please stay and play with me for a while.
101410.feeling1: Stanly is now operating in disappointment mode! Hmph!
101410.propose: Commander, your hand, please... Good, connection complete! From now on, we will be able to communicate telepathically! Heehee, do you feel how happy I am?
101410.drop_descrip: Fletcher-class destroyer - Stanly , Hull Number DD-478.
101410.profile: In the past, I've escorted many of my allies, and served in the Battle of Empress Augusta Bay as a member of the Little Beaver Squadron. As long as I'm in my serious mode, I'm really reliable in both day and night battles.
101410.touch2: Sorry to disappoint, but I don't have a hot and bothered mode.
101410.mission: I wish I had some mode that would let me skip the daily grind...
101410.home: Yo... When'd you get back, Commander? Stanly's rest mode still needs a while to run its course.
101410.expedition: Next time you're sending a commission, let Stanly handle the escort duty!
couple_encourage: This is the Little Beavers' justice mode!
101410.mail: There's a news update! Don't say I didn't tell you!
101410.feeling3: The other members of the Little Beaver Squad are fun to hang out with, but I still have the best time when I'm with you, Commander!
101410.lose: Crap, gotta switch to retreat mode pronto!

101340.detail: Phew! That feels great! The warm sunshine feels amazing today!
101340.touch: How about it? I've got a super healthy tan, right? Commander, show me ours~
101340.login: Right on time~! I just finished warming up~ Let's get going!
101340.battle: All righty! Let's set sail, everyone!
101340.feeling2: There are lots of girls here who like to run fast. That's why I'd like to race them!
101340.mission_complete: Woo! That's one more checked off the list! Way to go, Commander!
101340.main: These sunburns are battle scars from my active lifestyle! |Hey Bush, stop loafing around and come jog with me! |If only we could host a port-wide sports meet... I know I'd be the fastest one out of all my sisters!
101340.feeling5: I see you, Commander! Heheh~♪ Are you gonna get in trouble if I cling to you too much? But it feels so good... so can I keep doing it a bit more? Yaay~!
101340.unlock: Gotcha! Hehe, I'm Hazelwood, from the Fletcher class! Pleased to meet you!
101340.feeling4: The sun isn't coming out today... But no matter, hehe! As long as I stick with you, I won't get mopey at all~!
101340.feeling1: Everyone's saying to stay away from the commander... I wonder why?
101340.propose: From now on, I'll cling to you even more, Commander! ...Hehe, Commander, you're nice and warm... rub against me more~
101340.drop_descrip: Fletcher-class destroyer – Hazelwood, Hull Number DD-531.
101340.profile: I have a lot of experience on the battlefield, so I guess I'm a bit of a veteran! Oh right, I also served as a "reserve aviation command ship" for a while! What's that, you ask? Well, that'd be a ship that helps carriers guide their planes! Something like that~
101340.touch2: Eek! Don't go peeking under there!
101340.mission: Don't back down, no matter how intimidating your pile of work looks!
101340.home: Are you tired? Should I help you get comfortable?
101340.win_mvp: I'm number one? Now that's what I call unexpected, ehehe...
101340.expedition: A commission has finished? I'll be right back!
101340.mail: Whaddya think? Nobody gets the mail faster than me, right!
101340.feeling3: There's nothing more relaxing than soaking in the sunlight! Commander, you come with me too~!
101340.lose: I can't hold out any longer!

502029.detail: In order to save money, I'll have to cook with the most affordable ingredients I can get... Commander, come taste test this for me~
502029.touch: Where in the world did Bunbun get these fancy glasses... I hope he's not trying to become a pandit.
502029.main: Commander, if I catch you slacking off, you'll get a taste of my new karate chops. |If I don't cheer up a bit, who is Commander and Pinghai going to depend on- Ah, I didn't mean it like that! |Commander, don't just sit there all day, come here and do some aerobics with me to loosen up!
502029.unlock: Yes! … this feels good. Thank you, Commander. In order to live up to your expectations, from now on, I will be more serious around you, Commander. Hey, don't run!
502029.drop_descrip: Yes! … this feels good. Thank you, Commander. In order to live up to your expectations, from now on, I will be more serious around you, Commander. Hey, don't run!

301611.touch: Commander, you won't find the answer underneath my skirt.
301611.login: Commander, were you able to solve that question from yesterday?
301611.battle: Hm, hm... at this range, with these forces... we can win!
301611.main: Urakaze, Isokaze, Tanikaze, have you all taken your seats? Then let's review the essentials of the last formula we studied.|Improve yourself so that you can better protect those you care about. That's why I study as hard as I do.|Here we'll use this equation, then do this... Hah, a trivial question like this is no issue for me.
301611.unlock: Learning is exciting. The joy of acquiring new knowledge, the sense of achievement from solving difficult problems... you'll understand once you try it. So, shall we study together, Commander?
301611.drop_descrip: Learning is exciting. The joy of acquiring new knowledge, the sense of achievement from solving difficult problems... you'll understand once you try it. So, shall we study together, Commander?
301611.touch2: Commander, take your reading more seriously!

900282.detail: Need me to explain the details?
900282.login: Ah, Commander, you're back! I was just tidying up the documents, please have a look.
900282.battle: Mmm... I'm looking forward to everyone finishing their work too~!
900282.feeling2: The weather is pretty nice. Want to take a walk, Commander? Let's relax and chat for a while. What do you think?
900282.mission_complete: Here are your mission rewards. Let's take a look!
900282.main: I'm here to help you with anything you need.|If the Commander doesn't mind, please allow me to keep you company!|Commander, if you keep slacking off, even I will get angry.
900282.feeling5: Commander, want to have dinner together tonight? I'll make your favorite dish... Hmm? it's not a holiday or something like that... I just thought of it just now... If you want, Commander, we can do it every night~.
900282.upgrade: I hope you're looking forward to my performance from here on out!
900282.unlock: Hello, I'm Rodney. I shall be in your care from this day forward.
900282.feeling4: Not respecting the chain of command can mean big trouble, it has happened before……Of course it's ok for us since we're so close~
900282.propose: Everyday I spend with the Commander is a special day, I hope days like these will last forever.
900282.skill: There's no need to be polite when dealing with enemies.
900282.profile:
I'm Nelson's little sister, Rodney! Um... us sisters are pretty famous right?
 Erm, you've heard that my fighting style is unbefitting of my appearance? Well well, Commander, such rumors are, of course, false~
900282.touch2: Please don't do this in the command room...
900282.mission: Commander, shall we complete our new mission?
900282.home: Let me make a cup of tea~
900282.win_mvp: Hmm, I think I accidentally wasted a lot of ammunition...
900282.expedition: Hehe, Commander. The girls are back from commission!
couple_encourage: Hood, It's not good to hesitate!
It's no good to underestimate your opponents, my sister
Team Akatsuki? Let's do our best together!
900282.mail: I've brought your new mail, Commander.
900282.feeling3: Commander sure is gentle, always slowing down to match my pace when we're taking walks... I'm moved by details like this.
900282.lose: I can still fight... but we should probably retreat, for now...

301860.detail: I like being alone in my own room. What exactly do I do in my free time? ...I'm not telling you.
301860.touch: Commander... What are you up to? (Kazagumo throws you a suspicious look.)
301860.login: *Yawn*... Oh. You scared away the birdies, Commander.
301860.feeling2: You want to be friends with me? Okay, but if I find out you're planning something bad... then I'll never talk to you again.
301860.headtouch: I'm not a pet, so don't treat me like one...
301860.mission_complete: Mission complete. Wonder if I'll get a reward for my efforts...
301860.main: Could you not stare at me like that, Commander? I can't focus like this...|You're on duty, so no chit-chatting with me allowed, okay? ...I mean, if you feel really lonely, then maybe...|I like the satisfying toot-toot noise that recorders make... Do you wanna hear it? It'll have to be later, not now...
301860.feeling5: You're fun to be with, Commander. A lot of fun. In fact, you're my best friend... Hehehe~ I wanna always be with you. Always.
301860.unlock: Kazagumo, Yuugumo-class, reporting for duty. I hope I'll be able to get along well with everyone else here... Commander, you're not cooking up some dastardly plan, are you? You look rather questionable...
301860.feeling4: There have been rumors of this girl with long hair and skin as pale as a ghost's who appears out of nowhere at port... In fact, I think she's right behind you, Commander... What do you mean that's not gonna fool you? Well, I thought I'd just spook you a little...
301860.feeling1: I guess we're all fated to be alone. You, me, and everyone else...
301860.propose: I think... this is when you promise to never leave me. First you say it, then it's my turn... Hehehe~ Thank you. I love you.
301860.skill: I wanna get this over with...
301860.profile: Kazagumo, Yuugumo-class destroyer number 3. I served the 10th Destroyer Squadron, mostly running transport missions and naval evacuations. These little birdies are my friends. My hobbies? I'm not telling you.
301860.mission: Look at all these unfinished missions... You should really do something about them.
301860.home: Good going, Commander... You heard a strange noise just now? Uhh... I'm sure it was just your imagination.
301860.win_mvp: It'd be great if we could keep winning...
301860.expedition: The commission team's back. Don't forget to say hi to them... Me? Uhh, I think I'll stay right here.
couple_encourage: I'll keep you safe, Hiryuu.
Watch beneath the waves, Makinami.
301860.mail: Mail for the commander? Okay birdies, go fetch... No, please don't fight over who gets to do it.
301860.feeling3: You're not a bad person, so we can be friends... Do I wish I had more friends? I'm... not gonna tell you.
301860.lose: Ugh. I'm really out of it today...

107220.detail: I'm prepared to battle at nighttime, if necessary.
107220.login: Today's training and routine missions are progressing smoothly, Commander. You can rest easy.
107220.battle: Stay focused and be on your guard!
107220.hp_warning: How many... How many chances at victory do we have left?
107220.feeling2: You're curious how nighttime carrier battles look? Got it. I'll inform you next time there's one on the exercise schedule.
107220.mission_complete: We've got to stay diligent even after all our missions are complete.
107220.main: Should I call Cleveland... "Cleve"? Or do I keep it simple?|I will take on that task you assigned me with the highest priority, Commander.|I'm apparently terrible at reading between the lines... So please, Commander: whenever you have something to say, tell it to me straight.
107220.feeling5: "There are some things you can't express through words"...? I don't follow. If you don't tell people how you feel, how would they know? For instance, how would you be able to guess that I love you if I didn't say it directly?
107220.upgrade: How about we set up a naval exercise right away?
107220.unlock: I'm Independence, light carrier. Don't worry about that "light" part, and just hand those missions over to me.
107220.feeling4: Isn't there something you want to tell me? Be it combat-related, or anything else. Why do I ask? Because I want to know what sort of place I have in your heart.
107220.feeling1: Allow me to be blunt: what the hell is wrong with you?
107220.propose: It's thanks to our fateful encounter at the crossroads of life that I found the place where I belong... Was that... a weird way to put it? Umm, well, you know what I mean. I just can't find the right words... In any case, I'm happy to be together with you!
107220.drop_descrip: Independence-class light aircraft carrier – Independence, Hull Number CVL-22.
107220.profile: I was initially to be the fifth Cleveland-class cruiser, but got remodeled into a light aircraft carrier due to the skyrocketing need for additional carriers. Thanks to the new capabilities this gave me, I flourished in battle and achieved victory together with my allies.
107220.touch2: Go to the Admiralty and explain yourself. Right now.
107220.mission: A new mission has come in. Let's get it done ASAP.
107220.home: Should we draft a plan for the next operation?
107220.expedition: The goods from that commission have arrived. Saves us time having to carry it by hand.
couple_encourage: Cleveland... Or should I say "Cleve"?
Night Carrier Division, assemble!
Task Force 38 is operational!
107220.mail: I've brought your mail. Give it a read.
107220.feeling3: A CVL might never rival an ordinary CV in terms of sheer power, but... I just want you to recognize what I'm capable of.

302109.detail: I look even cooler now when I don't say anything? Whatever... have it your way...
302109.touch: Maybe I should go practice using this naginata or something...
302109.login: Commander, you're back. Huh? I just happen to remember what your footsteps sound like.
302109.battle: There are people waiting for me... so I refuse to lose!
302109.main: Recently, Mikuma has been telling me that I have more self-esteem... Not sure about that one though, I don't think I've really changed... |Secretary ship duties? Well, I still think I'm not really cut out for it compared to the others... but if it's what you want, I'll keep doing it. |Commander, be honest. What do you think about my new outfit after the retrofit? Um... if you like it, I suppose we can keep it like this...
302109.unlock: Are you sure this is a retrofit and not some weird hazing ritual? I look... Well, I suppose I do feel stronger. Guess I'll try to work a bit harder. Wouldn't hurt for you to look forward to it a little.
302109.drop_descrip: Are you sure this is a retrofit and not some weird hazing ritual? I look... Well, I suppose I do feel stronger. Guess I'll try to work a bit harder. Wouldn't hurt for you to look forward to it a little.

107290.detail: Commander, such perfect timing. I was just performing some maintenance on this little one. Would you mind lending a hand?
107290.touch: I have a lovely smile? Um, well... ehehe... I'm glad my smile cheers you up, Commander.
107290.login: At last, you've made your return, Commander. Now, let us begin the day's labors, shall we?
107290.battle: Onward without fear! For I stand behind you with all my might!
107290.feeling2: Perfect. Our work goes exactly according to plan... Yes, now on to next month's plan...
107290.main: To make a beautiful plan and then watch it come together – is there any better way to get one's work done? Commander, why not give my way a try?|This little one is a Hellcat, endlessly useful in so many battles. Hehe.|Maybe there's nothing really special about me, I'm not the type to stand out in a crowd, but I... as long as I can do things my way, and be helpful to everyone, that's good enough for me. Hehehe.
107290.feeling5: Whether I'm happy or sad, you're always here with me, Commander... I, why I might just be the luckiest girl in the world... Hehehe.
107290.upgrade: Now I can be so much more useful to everyone. Thank you very much, Commander.
107290.unlock: Bataan of the Eagle Union's Independence-class, at your service. If you don't mind, when forming a fleet for a sortie... please consider including me! I may not be flawless, but I should be able to handle a combat mission or two!
107290.feeling4: It seems we've been spending a lot more alone time together lately, Commander... It's okay if we get even more intimate... is it? Well, then... If I sit a little closer... even cuddle up a bit... is that... okay too?
107290.feeling1: No one respects a worthless commander. You need to shape up! Come, I'll help you.
107290.propose: To be here with you, Commander, celebrating a day like this... I can't fathom how lucky I am. I can't even begin to know what to say... Commander, umm, do you think you could close your eyes for me for a second...?
107290.drop_descrip: Independence-class light aircraft carrier – Bataan, Hull Number CVL-29.
107290.skill: Now it's your turn, little planes. Be sa~fe!
107290.profile: I am the Independence-class light aircraft carrier Bataan of the Eagle Union. I participated in numerous battles during the world war. I will resolutely provide all necessary aid and support to all the ships of this fleet, as is my duty.
107290.touch2: My, Commander, you can be such a child sometimes...
107290.mission: If you don't complete your missions, you won't get any stronger. Come, Commander, just a little bit more effort and we'll clear those missions off the board.
107290.home: Welcome back, Commander. You certainly fought hard. If you have need of me, I would be happy to accompany you on the next sortie.
107290.win_mvp: Am I... the MVP? Ahahaha... this victory belongs to all of us together.
107290.expedition: The ships you sent out on commission have returned. Shall we go greet them?
107290.mail: The mail is here. Take a look, please, Commander.
107290.feeling3: How will I spend my day off? I suppose I'll just lounge around by myself. That's how I like to relax, after all. It's not like I have any particular hobbies or anything... Aha, ahaha...
107290.lose: Hm... I must carry this lesson on to the next battle...

900279.detail:
D-don't look at me inappropriatly! And do your work properly! 
--Y-Y-You were just looking at my bridge?! ...Ahaha...
900279.touch: Hwaa!? Commander... S...Stop... is what you want me to say?!
900279.login: Can I conduct combat operations since the weather is so nice today, Commander?
900279.battle: Everyone, the one with the lowest results will get extra lessons~~
900279.feeling2: Why are kids today thinking about weird things all the time...!
900279.mission_complete: The compensation... is nothing major, but it's not good to neglect it either.
900279.main: What I teach besides fighting is human se... I-I mean... physical education!|The Sakura Empire? ...Uh, Uhhh... I- I don't know enough to teach you about that!|If you don't listen to what I say, I'll punish you!
900279.feeling5: Commander, you're really helpless without me. S-so... I-I'm... I'm holding you back for another year!
900279.upgrade: I, Ms. Ranger, am going to teach you some more things
900279.feeling4: T-T-Teacher-student relationships?!! I've never thought about such things; I've never even read those kinds of books before. I totally, totally never look forward to that!
900279.propose: *cries*... Receiving such a precious thing from a student, and getting so happy to the point of shedding tears... I, Ranger, am a failure as an educator...
900279.drop_descrip: Ranger-class aircraft carrier ー Ranger, Hull Number CV-4!
900279.touch2: D-don't tell anyone about this! You'll embarrass me!
900279.mission: Finish your missions properly. Otherwise, there will be catch up lessons!
900279.home: Have you finished your homework? Alright. Then as promised, I'll give you a reward~
900279.win_mvp: Commander, you must not become worn out quickly like the enemy-- Oh no... not like that!
900279.expedition: Mr. Commander~ You forgot to check the results. You might see the girls become angry at you.
900279.mail: You've got mail. Do you want me to hold your hand through teaching you how to reply? AAH! Not literally!
900279.feeling3: Commander, you are a capable child if you are put into action. I feel a little happy.
900279.lose: I can't let you see me like this, Commander.....

301861.detail: I've practiced some more. I'll play you a song, if you'll listen... On second thought, maybe I won't.
301861.touch: Ugh... I lost track of the tempo because of that... Thanks, meanie.
301861.login: Zzz... What is it, Commander...? Me? The breeze was just too nice and I fell asleep...
301861.main: Weird... I played pretty well just a moment ago, but now I can't do it...|The name of the song I just played? I'm not gonna tell you right now. After I've mastered it, all right?|You're so nice, hanging out with me even after school... I'm not taking up your time, am I?
301861.unlock: Toot~♪ Oh, Commander, did you hear me practicing my recorder? Umm, I'd appreciate it if you didn't tell the others.
301861.drop_descrip: Toot~♪ Oh, Commander, did you hear me practicing my recorder? Umm, I'd appreciate it if you didn't tell the others.
301861.touch2: Oh... Seriously, Commander? You're messing up my melody.
301861.home: Welcome back, Commander. You didn't bring company... did you? Okay, good. I don't want others to hear how not-good I am at the recorder...

102132.touch: Are we heading out? Ahah, then let me get out my umbrella. Hey, come closer, otherwise you'll get snow on your clothes.
102132.login: You should drink a little something to warm yourself up before getting to work.
102132.main: A "hatsumode," huh... Do you have any wishes to make, Commander? It so happens I don't, so you can have my wish.|Not to say the Eagle Union's new year celebrations are lonesome, but the Sakura Empire's and Eastern Radiance definitely celebrate New Year's with more festivity. And I like festivities.|Oh, Commander, if you're hoping to get me drunk... well, it depends on how much you yourself can drink. Ahahah~
102132.feeling5: Hmm... seems it'll keep snowing for a while. Why don't you stay for the night, Commander? ...Oh? I was thinking we could share some drinks, but perhaps you had something else in mind? Ahahah♡
102132.unlock: The Sakura Empire's clothes are just so refined. Ahaha... Aren't you cold standing out there, Commander? Sit down with me and have a drink.
102132.drop_descrip: The Sakura Empire's clothes are just so refined. Ahaha... Aren't you cold standing out there, Commander? Sit down with me and have a drink.
102132.home: Welcome back. I've put on the heater for you. Oh, me? I'd like to stay here and enjoy the snow a little longer.

202202.detail: Worry not, for I have come prepared for every occasion. Food, drinks, magazines, sunscreen, contingency combat armaments, life-saving equipment, and... a cat? Why are you here? ...Oh, umm, I was just talking to myself!
202202.touch: My honourable Master, allow me to protect you from the sun.
202202.login: No matter where we are, I shall do my utmost to keep you safe. My honourable Master, simply enjoy yourself, however you please.
202202.main: My honourable Master, why are you staring at me so intently? Did this humble maid err somewhere?! ...I'm overthinking things...? |Swimming? If... if you wouldn't mind teaching me... Um, sorry, a lowly maid has no right to request your valuable time... |My honourable Master, are you tired? Something to rest on...? ...Um, if you wouldn't mind, then... feel free to use my body...!
202202.unlock: I've received ample advice from my colleagues in the Maid Team regarding swimwear etiquette. My honourable Master, are you pleased with my appearance?
202202.drop_descrip: I've received ample advice from my colleagues in the Maid Team regarding swimwear etiquette. My honourable Master, are you pleased with my appearance?
202202.touch2: Understood. If you would like to see me in a bikini, then... Is, is that so? I'm terribly sorry... I prematurely jumped to conclusions yet again.

102070.detail: The... old injury to my foot? Well... my foot's still a bit stiff, but I won't ever let myself drag everyone else down...!
102070.touch: Pl... please be gentle... I'm very susceptible to pain...
102070.login: C-Commander... I'll always be w-waiting for you here...
102070.battle: Everyone... look after yourselves... and watch out for those mean submarines...
102070.feeling2: I... often have nightmares about five brothers whose faces are all blurred, and they tell me to come with them... It's really scary...
102070.mission_complete: I don't need any rewards... just being here with everyone is enough for me...
102070.main: *Eek* Commander?! Y-you scared me...|I want to be brave... But it's really hard...|Commander, have I annoyed you in any way...?
102070.feeling5: Now when I dream about those five brothers... I can see their faces clearly, and they bless me with their smiles... But somehow it was so sad it almost made me cry... *Tearful sobbing*... Can I really live happily together with you, Commander? It's not just a dream, right...?
102070.unlock: I-I'm Juneau... I'm a cruiser... I'm scared of pain... *Sob* And I'm scared of you, Commander...!
102070.feeling4: I'm not afraid of having nightmares anymore... b-but can I still sleep together with you, Commander...?
102070.feeling1: Don't come near me! ...Sorry, I think you're a little scary, Commander...
102070.propose: ...Mhm, I have faith in you, Commander... I told the people in my dreams that I've found happiness and would do my best to live on for their sake as well... I'm truly... truly happy right now...
102070.drop_descrip: Atlanta-class light cruiser – Juneau, Hull Number CL-52!
102070.skill: Me too! I-I'll give it my best shot!
102070.profile: I-I'm Juneau, an Atlanta-class anti-aircraft cruiser... Because I have high anti-air capabilities, I was assigned to a Task Force, but I'm actually scared of getting shot... Unfortunately I couldn't make it back home from Espiritu Santo...
102070.mission: What? A mission? I don't mind as long as we aren't fighting submarines...
102070.home: I'm really hoping this war will end soon... Once it's over, let's all go someplace together...
102070.win_mvp: Phew... I almost got hit... *Sob*... I don't care about being the MVP... I'm just trying my best so I can come home in one piece...
102070.expedition: Umm... Commander... there's a commission that's been completed...
102070.mail: Commander... excuse me... here's your mail...
102070.feeling3: Commander, can I go to bed with you again tonight? ... I feel very safe when I sleep next to you...
102070.lose: That hurts! ... I can't feel my left foot... Someone come save me....!

301179.drop_descrip: The newly-retrofitted Kagerou has arrived~ I won't let that sister of mine pass me up anymore! Commander, lead us forward towards distant shores!

502022.touch: The whole family's all gathered for the Mid-Autumn Festival! Happy holidays, Commander!
502022.main: Oh gosh, mooncake! Yes! Om nom nom nom!|It's a holiday, so nobody will mind if I drink a little... right? *gulp*, *gulp*... Ahahaha... Something here smells like sweet osmanthus~!|Da Bao, Baobao, do you want some mooncake too? Here you go.
502022.unlock: Happy Mid-Autumn Festival! By the way, I heard that if you prayed to the moon today, you'll become as pretty as the Goddess of the Moon! ...Eh, you're really doing it?!
502022.drop_descrip: Happy Mid-Autumn Festival! By the way, I heard that if you prayed to the moon today, you'll become as pretty as the Goddess of the Moon! ...Eh, you're really doing it?!
502022.touch2: For the last time! I'm not a bunny girl, I'm a moon rabbit! Got it?!

903020.detail: When it comes to history, relying on second-hand accounts is not enough to sift fact from fiction. You must conduct your own research.
903020.touch: Oh my, did you want to slack off for a bit? Hehe, I won't tell anyone else, so take some time off, okay?
903020.login: We're on great terms after all. I would've been fine waiting a bit longer.
903020.battle: It'd be nice if the battle goes the way we want it to.
903020.hp_warning: I'm telling you, the constraints of the treaty are still too suffocatingly restrictive...
903020.feeling2: Are you a bit scared of me? Hehe, don't worry, Commander. I wouldn't harm an ally.
903020.headtouch: Are you trying to see if I have a fever...?
903020.mission_complete: Have you finished the mission? Good work. Please leave the report to me and go get some rest.
903020.main: Even if I don’t have any honors or decorations, my strength can speak for itself. | Oh, Commander. How about enjoying some wine with me later? Hehe, only after you finish up the rest of your work though, alright? | Gold...? Oh, were you interested in that story? Hehehe. At that time, the Iris were... | My hobby is touring cat cafés, but this port doesn't... Oh, that's right. Even at this port, there are plenty of adorable creatures... Yes, how lovely! | The Royal Navy are now allies who fight together with us. Furthermore... even yesterday's enemies are today's allies. What an interesting life this has been... Hehehe.
903020.feeling5: Commander... would you like to rely on me? ...If it's you, I'd be happy to let you rely on me, and I'd always be supporting you from your side. Hehe, in exchange... I hope you'll show me just how much you can achieve, with me by your side.
903020.upgrade: Shattering the confines of the treaty... is rather pleasurable. Hehehe~
903020.unlock: Bonjour. From today, this heavy cruiser of the Vichya Dominion shall now be serving at this port. It's a pleasure to meet you, hehe. If it's not too much to ask, I hope that we can get along well.
903020.feeling4: You know, I actually really, really like cute things. Those trinkets, those squishy furballs, making sweets... Hehe, don't you think it's nice for an adult to enjoy cute things?
903020.feeling1: Oh, Commander. I've been looking into the documents that need to be prepared for your formal retirement. Are you ready to start the process?
903020.propose: Thank you. Henceforth, I vow to dedicate my whole heart and body to you. Together, let us enjoy - slowly and surely - just how sweet our future will be. My partner, my beloved...
903020.profile: I'm the flagship of the Vichya's First Cruiser Fleet, Algérie of the Templar Knights. In my history as a ship... I was called the best-designed treaty cruiser. Accordingly, I've been through plenty of interesting escapades... Hehehe. How do you feel about me, Commander?
903020.touch2: Commander~? No matter how nice the other person may be, you shouldn't get too carried away. Hehe.
903020.mission: We've just received a new directive from the higher-ups. Oh? It seems that you're just as busy as always... As much as I'd like to do some of this work in your stead, I suppose I wouldn't be able to?
903020.home: Good work planning out the operation, Commander. How would you like some freshly brewed coffee?
903020.win_mvp: If only you realized the situation you were in a little sooner, you might've been able to avoid this outcome... but what can you do at this point?
903020.expedition: The girls from the commission team have come back. I wonder if I can guess which girl's carrying the most important goods?
couple_encourage: There's nothing to fear. The Vichya Dominion rises up to face any crisis.
We've finally got a chance to compete, Zara. Wanna see who's better?
Hehe, what a nice smell. Will you let me tag along for a bit?
903020.mail: Reading a letter allows you to peek into the hidden heart of the person who sent it... Hehehe, how exciting! Here, Commander, some new mail's come in for you.
903020.feeling3: Commander, won't you drink a little with me? Are you perhaps bad at holding your alcohol? That's alright. Just take a little sip, like this... and try slowly tasting it with your throat... That's it... Don't you taste it?... The cool, rich flavor of maturity.
903020.lose: It seems that I lost... But don't worry, Commander. Let's prepare carefully and try again.

900280.detail: Commander, if you keep looking at me like that, you’ll be eaten up.
900280.login: Justice and righteousness are for the strong only. The weak can only weep in vain.
900280.battle: Entertain me with your final struggles. Hehehe...
900280.hp_warning: It’s time for a death match! Heheh- hehehe!
900280.feeling2: The weak will be eliminated. If you cannot accept that, then simply become stronger.
900280.mission_complete: Here are the rewards, the fruits of your labor.
900280.main: I shall conquer all, no matter who stands against me.|Our enemies may be strong, but that is what makes them worth crushing. Heheh...|The girls of the Fifth Carrier Division? They might amount to something if they work hard enough.
900280.feeling5: I have so much I want to say, but I forget them all the moment I see your face...
900280.upgrade: Not bad. I’ve come up with some new combat techniques.
900280.unlock: Will I be able to find a worthy foe here? Very well. I’m yours. Perhaps this, too, is destiny.
900280.feeling4: I cannot comprehend these emotions... is this some sort of primal instinct?
900280.feeling1: It seems like you're not the hero I was looking for...
900280.propose: ... Is this for me? Hm... perhaps it is fate for the strong to be drawn to each other. If that is the case, I shall follow my instincts then. Hehehe~
900280.skill: Only the strong may survive on the battlefield!
900280.profile: I am {namecode:92}, from the First Carrier Division. I was originally designed to be a battleship, but fate had different plans or me. Enemies? I simply slaughter them, but only because it is my duty, not for fun.
900280.touch2: ... Fine. If you say it helps you relax...
900280.mission: Commander, stop slacking around. There are still missions to complete.
900280.home: A fitting reward for the ears of our enemies. Let us enjoy the spoils of war leisurely.
900280.win_mvp: Such is the fate of the weak. Death, nothing more.
900280.expedition: The girls on commission have returned. Go on ahead, I will prepare some refreshments for them.
couple_encourage: Sister, please take this seriously.
The First Carrier Division is not to be looked down upon!
I did not expect to be fighting alongside you all...
900280.mail: Your mail is here. Try not to forget it next time.
900280.feeling3: Should you be defeated one day, it simply means that you were too weak. That much is a fact of nature. Though... because you are mine, I would at least avenge you.
900280.lose: This pain... I shall return it tenfold!

903021.detail: Hehehe. Commander, it seemed like you enjoyed being surrounded by so many cute girls. Who caught your attention the most?
903021.touch: You want some coconut juice...? Alright, wait there for now. I'll bring some over.
903021.login: Even if you've already applied some sunscreen, you still need to take care to not get sunburns.
903021.main: Here, a sun cap. If you want to play out on the beach, please make the proper preparations against the sun's rays first.|A beach volleyball match between the Vichya and Royal Navy... Sounds fun. How about watching it together?|nil|Writing words on the beach and waiting for the waves to wash them away... Hehe, seems like it'd be fun~ What shall we write?|Sigh... It's seriously quite hot... Commander, don't push yourself, you hear? Please let me know if you start to feel worse.
903021.feeling5: Commander, if I buried you in the sand neck-down, you wouldn't be able to move, and I'd be able to do whatever I want to you~ Hehehe, I'm joking. Or, would you like to do that to me? Hehehehe.
903021.unlock: Oh my, hehe... Are you enjoying the warmth of the sunlight here? I'm glad that you're finding some time to relax here, but wouldn't you rather come play with everyone else?
903021.drop_descrip: Oh my, hehe... Are you enjoying the warmth of the sunlight here? I'm glad that you're finding some time to relax here, but wouldn't you rather come play with everyone else?
903021.touch2: Huh?! I wonder, do these clothes make the Commander more impertinent...?
903021.home: Wine... would be a little bit out of place here. Hehe. Commander, will some tropical juice suffice?

301180.detail: ... Touch me in the wrong way and you will die.
301180.login: Could one say "long time no see," perhaps...?
301180.battle: Allow me to show you all my combat techniques...
301180.feeling2: I am the polar opposite of {namecode:19}… If she is light then I am shadow. Commander? Yes, of course, you are a big fool. I do not hate her, but who knows if I hate you…?
301180.mission_complete: "Rewards" have arrived… Ah, do not task me with collecting them, you may do it yourself.
301180.main: Floating…|I am bad at dealing with hotheads.|You're standing beside me because I have a "cooling aura"…? Are you an idiot?
301180.feeling5: *Sigh*... Would it not have been better if I could have been your guardian angel instead… Then I could always intervene… I mean, "protect" you when need be.
301180.upgrade: You certainly are a big fool, spending such precious resources on me…
301180.unlock: I am {namecode:20}, the second ship of the {namecode:19}-class... I humbly ask for your kind treatment, Commander.
301180.feeling4: What an idiotic, troublesome commander you are, wishing to make everyone happy… I simply cannot let your stupidity go unsupervised.
301180.feeling1: There exists no cure for your stupidity...
301180.propose: *Sigh*… I never imagined a ghost could be brought here. Are you really just as foolish as you appear, Commander? Or have you seen too many of these strange so called "movies"? … Oh well, there is nothing wrong with this, so I shall keep your gift secure.
301180.skill: O, will-o'-wisps, join me for this strike...
301180.profile: I am the {namecode:19}-class... or rather, the second ship of the {namecode:20}-class, {namecode:20}. People mistakenly think my name refers to ghosts, but it is merely the name of a natural phenomena. I personally prefer to think of my appearance as a "cosplay"... That aside, I humbly ask for your kind treatment, you idio... my dear Commander.
301180.touch2: You have a thing for ghosts? You really are something...
301180.mission: It seems we have a new mission… However, I do not care either way.
301180.home: You may stare all you wish, but it will not make me start floating...
301180.win_mvp: I never imaged they would be this weak…
301180.expedition: I waited 1 whole minute for you, yet you did not realize that a commission had been completed… It really is true, you are a big fool who cannot do anything if I am not around.
301180.mail: You seem to have "mail"… I should not have to help you with this too...
