301180.feeling3: I will come in the dead of night and devour you soul… I said, and you actually believed it? It was in fact my embers that chased away so many pests, and yet you thought I would harm you? You tremendous fool…

101411.detail: The teacher didn't find out about the note I passed, right? Commander, don't you tattle on me, got it?
101411.touch: No peeking at a girl's secrets! That's off limits!
101411.login: Student Mode runs off of sugar! Ah, Commander, let's split this strawberry jam bun!
101411.main: With these note slips, you can chat with your friends in an otherwise boring class! Heheh~! |Smalley always heads straight to the dojo after class. Do you think she's permanently in "Combat Mode?" ... |I brought some more candy! After all, that's what Student Mode runs on!
101411.feeling5: Commander, there's mail for you! Will it be random doodles, or a girl's confession? You'll have to see for yourself! Bye bye!
101411.unlock: Stanly's brand new "Student Mode," activate! Commander, come check out my new look!
101411.drop_descrip: Stanly's brand new "Student Mode," activate! Commander, come check out my new look!
101411.touch2: Wait, I've seen enough to know where this is going...
101411.home: I'm down for a slightly longer recess~
101411.mail: This envelope with a heart on it sure is suspicious... Commander, who'd you get it from?

502025.detail: Yat Sen, Ping Hai, and I made this cake for the party, with the help of some other girls. It had to be big enough to feed everyone... But a big baozi probably would have been better than a big cake... Ahem! N-never mind.
502025.touch: Passing out the cake...? That's not a job for a commander! Leave it to me and Ping Hai, and of course Da Bao and Baobao!
502025.login: This cake is for you, Commander! T-take it!
502025.main: Da Bao! Bring the next slice over here! Pay attention!|I told her not to, but I'm still worried Ping Hai is going to gobble up the cake before she finishes passing it out... I better go keep an eye on her!|While handing out all this cake I realized just how many friends Ping Hai and I have made lately... Heh heh.
502025.unlock: Yat Sen said this look would be best for a party, but, is it really okay? I'm not used to having my hair down like this...
502025.drop_descrip: Yat Sen said this look would be best for a party, but, is it really okay? I'm not used to having my hair down like this...
502025.touch2: Waaah! C-Commander! What if I drop the cake?!
502025.home: A party this fancy must have cost a lot... Hm... Fine! The money's spent, so we might as well enjoy ourselves!

201210.detail: Commander, you care so much about me... I'm so very happy!
201210.battle: This seems like a good way to kill time!
201210.hp_warning: Everyone, let's work hard! For the commander's sake!
201210.feeling2: ...I'm cute? ...Eeeeh~! You're lying, right? Commander, are you trying to trick me again~
201210.mission_complete: Commander, Commander! Let's go check out the rewards!
201210.main: Let's work hard for the whole day!|Fwa... I don't like to feel nonexistent. I'm gonna strike back~|I'm very lucky!|Commander, Commander, let's play with me~!|Commander... it feels safe by your side~
201210.feeling5: Being together with you makes me so happy, Commander~ Ah, I made a boxed meal. Do you want to try some?
201210.upgrade: Hehe, your care is very heart-warming, Commander!
201210.unlock: I'm Javelin, Commander. Nice to meet you. Oh ho? You look like you have no idea what to do with a girl of your type being assigned to you!
201210.feeling4: Commander, you see, I want to be confessed to under the legendary tree like in comics~ and stuff...
201210.feeling1: Commander, if you don't behave yourself, I am going to start disliking you. You hear me?
201210.propose: Commander, what's wrong? Your face looks frozen... Eh? ... Wait, my heart isn't ready... what to do, what to do, my hair is messy and I haven't put on any makup or a dress... Commander, wait for me! Definitely wait for me!
201210.drop_descrip: J-class destroyer ー Javelin, Hull Number F61!
201210.profile:
Good day, Commander! I'm the J class destroyer Javelin! 
My sisters and I were part of the Narvik battle and the evacuation of Dunkirk! I had a little trouble along the way, but I fought until the very end!
201210.touch2: Kyaa~! Commander, perverted behaviour is bad!
201210.mission: Commander, Commander, new missions have been issued!
201210.home: Great work, Commander. Do you want a back massage?
201210.win_mvp: Am I amazing? Oh you shouldn't have~ But, please learn how to do a better job praising me!
201210.expedition: Getting tired? The commissions should be done just around this time. Shall we go to the docks to welcome them back?
couple_encourage: Witness the power of the J-class!
Let's work hard for the Commander!
Kaede's Legion, fight!
201210.feeling3: I've gotten closer to you now, Commander. Hehehe. But I'm gonna have to work harder~
201210.lose: Ugh... I let my guard down...

207060.detail: Expect great things for me, for I am Glorious! Of... of course! I'll be your glory forever!
207060.login: Today is a good day. Good weather puts you in a good mood to get work done!
207060.feeling2: You can't be too careful in war... That being said...
207060.mission_complete: I won't forget this time... *ahem* Commander, collect your rewards!
207060.main: Ardent and Acasta did the best they could, but I...|I'll be more prudent in the future. Only then can I avoid meeting disaster again!|Commander, glory and courage go hand in hand. However, Courage isn't the same thing as recklessness.
207060.feeling5: Commander, if you are tired you can always rest in my embrace. Eh? Didn't you say yesterday that was the best way for you to recover?
207060.upgrade: Thank you, but power alone is not enough to win...
207060.unlock: Royal Navy large crui– *ahem* aircraft carrier Glorious, reporting in! Commander, stand up straight, for your glory has arrived!
207060.feeling4: Commander, it's quite late. Why not rest a bit? I've made some black tea... Mail? It's in your tea, of course... *Zzzzz*
207060.feeling1: Commander, you're making me feel uncomfortable.
207060.propose: If we face it together, there is nothing we can't overcome, Commander. Are you ready to accept your Glory?
207060.drop_descrip: Courageous-class aircraft carrier – Glorious, Hull Number 77.
207060.skill: May victory and glory be ours... hopefully!
207060.profile: I'm the Royal Navy's heavy crui... *ahem* ex-cruiser, now aircraft carrier, Glorious! I was just being careless when I was sunk by Scharnhorst and Gneisenau, not because they're better than me!
207060.touch2: Commander, you're holding the glory of the Royal Navy
207060.mission: Rest up and then finish your missions in one go!
207060.home: You need to always keep your guard up, Commander.
207060.expedition: Commander, after your commissions are complete, you should... uh... hm... collect your rewards!
couple_encourage: This time, we fight together!
207060.mail: I'll put the tea here... Mail? Ah, yes! There's new mail for you!
207060.feeling3: The kids in the sky have been working very hard. Can't they rest with me for a while? ... ... Commander, in times of war, is there no room for warmth?
207060.lose: Next time, I'll scout out the enemy before we attack!

202203.detail: I made some Dragon Empery dishes, however they turned out quite... Pl-Please, do not be concerned! *This* year, I vow to make delectable food that shall suit the honourable Master's palate!
202203.touch: My perceptive Master, would there happen to be dust clinging to my dress...?
202203.login: Happy Lunar New Year, honourable Master. I have made a cup of tea for you.
202203.main: My honourable Master, if you'll forgive my asking, have you eaten any unusually shaped, unstuffed gyoza? ...P-Pardon me, I was merely wondering...|This naughty maid is deeply obliged to have the privilege of spending the holidays with her honourable Master.|nil
202203.unlock: I have heard it is part of a maid's duties to dress to her honourable Master's liking over the holidays. Would this outfit happen to... satisfy the honourable Master's wishes?
202203.drop_descrip: I have heard it is part of a maid's duties to dress to her honourable Master's liking over the holidays. Would this outfit happen to... satisfy the honourable Master's wishes?
202203.touch2: If you wish me to service you in these Dragon Empery garments, then... Oh, my apologies! I've made yet another careless assumption...
202203.home: My outfit is unsafe to wear in windy weather? Are you concerned with my wellbeing and would not want me catching a cold? Oh, honourable Master, your thoughtfulness humbles me!

301181.detail: Commander, did you come to help out? To thank you, I shall offer you a 20-percent discount on these mooncakes...
301181.touch: Commander, you'll have to pay for anything that you touch.
301181.login: Happy Mid-Autumn Festival... I hope I said that right...?
301181.main: Lotus seed mooncakes, osmanthus mooncakes, five-nut mooncakes... If it sells well, it's a good mooncake, wouldn't you agree?|These sky lanterns look just like the full moon tonight. Commander, would you like one? |These mooncakes are one hundred percent authentic, unlike the tech p... Err, I didn't say anything.
301181.feeling5: I heard that in the Dragon Empery, the Mid-Autumn Festival is a time to be reunited with your loved ones. Commander, are you going to go watch the moon with your favorite girl? ... You want to go with me? Saying that won't get you anywhere... Fine, Commander, as a token of my appreciation, I'll give you a 50% discount.
301181.unlock: I see a chance... to capitalize on the Dragon Empery's famous mooncakes... Commander, would you like to have a taste of the Moon Palace's delicacies? If you buy them in bulk, I'll give you a special discount.
301181.touch2: Commander, why don't you calm down with a nice cup of tea...? Poured on top of your head, that is.
301181.home: That dumb Akashi, why'd she have to go and order so many of these... when am I going to be able to clear out this stock...?

302120.detail: These bandages? They're not for when I get hurt, they're for wrapping around my fists... You'll struggle to find anyone who can actually injure me.
302120.touch: Commander, you'll end up gettin' hurt if you approach me without warning.
302120.login: I'm done warmin' up. Time to sortie, or what?
302120.feeling2: I'm not much of a people person, so I'd rather you'd just leave me alone... Hey, relax. You're my boss, so I'll still do my job.
302120.mission_complete: You sure you wanna ignore those mission rewards, Commander? Not that I really care.
302120.main: I dream of justice, justice for... Never mind. Let's write off that one as a joke.|All I have are my principles and my fists. Even so, I'll always keep moving forward.|Commander, who do you think is our worst enemy? The Sirens? I think it's our own minds.
302120.feeling5: People like you are pretty amazing. You do everything I want to, but just a bit better... When I'm with you, I even lose track of time... As long as you don't lose sight of who you are, I'll follow you to ends of the earth.
302120.unlock: You're a commander? I don't need one... But maybe we were fated to meet, or something. Guess you've got me to look after too, now. The name's Sendai. Don't forget it.
302120.feeling4: Feels like I've been here a long time... I know I'm the one saying that, but still, it really has been a long time...
302120.feeling1: Think it's about time we say goodbye.
302120.propose: Commander, before you gave me this, I'd just have left you if you'd forgotten your principles... But now that you've given me this... Forget your principles, and you'll taste my fists of love and rage. *Giggle*
302120.drop_descrip: Sendai-class light cruiser number one – Sendai.
302120.profile: I'm Sendai, the first ship of the Sendai-class. Although my service record isn't as impressive as my little sisters', I served as the flagship of Destroyer Squadron 3 and fought in tons of battles. I bit the dust at Bougainville, but I did so as a warrior with no regrets.
302120.touch2: You got a damn death wish? You askin' me to knock some sense into that skull of yours? Izzat it, huh?!
302120.mission: A mission... That's my kinda deal.
302120.home: When's the next sortie? I've still got a ton of spare bandages.
302120.win_mvp: Heh. Won't even need to replace my bandages.
302120.expedition: Yo, commission's done. Don't tell me you're really considering just keeping those hardworking girls waiting.
couple_encourage: Kako, stay close to me.
Jintsuu, what should I do?
302120.feeling3: I can't settle until I've made right out of wrong with my fists. That's my way of life. It's why I try not to get involved in anyone's business; I just don't wanna cause any trouble.
302120.lose: Owwww... Ahaha... Guess this is it...

107223.detail: Saratoga and Lexington do stretches on the regular, giving them great dexterity for aircraft carriers. They really live up to their rep as idols. Good examples of hard work paying off, too.
107223.touch: Yeah, that's it. Push on my back and hold it like that.
107223.login: Your health suffers if you don't move your muscles enough. Keep an eye on your posture in the office so you don't develop a hunchback, Commander.
107223.main: Who's the most dexterous among the Cleveland class? If I had to guess... Columbia. She does ballet, you know.|Even the most basic of stretches qualify as exercise. Though I'll admit, it's not very rigorous exercise.|Long Island claims mastering yoga gives you the power to breathe fire and extend your arms. I don't buy that idea, though.
107223.unlock: Whew... A bit of stretching helps keep the body flexible. Hm? I'm in loungewear, what about it? I'd appreciate it if you wouldn't stare too much, though...
107223.drop_descrip: Whew... A bit of stretching helps keep the body flexible. Hm? I'm in loungewear, what about it? I'd appreciate it if you wouldn't stare too much, though...
107223.touch2: I appreciate your help with the pushes, but now you're just pushing your luck.
107223.home: Feel like doing some stretches with me? I could use a hand with a couple of moves, like the forward bend for instance.

401461.drop_descrip: The bustling beach, clamoring with waves of joyfulness... experiencing this kind of summer is a first for me, but I don't dislike it...

102133.detail: Hehehe, you thought I'd drive in these high heels? It's certainly not impossible, but I'd rather use the other pair of shoes I have inside.
102133.touch: Let's see here... Ah, thanks, Commander. Hehehe, you're getting quite good at this.
102133.login: The view here is lovely~ Let's pull over for a moment to take in the winds of good luck.
102133.mission_complete: Oh, you went and claimed those mission rewards? You could've taken your time if you wanted. Hehehe~
102133.main: Oh dear, was that... Jamaica? Hehehe... Fasten your seatbelt, Commander. This'll be a bit of a wild ride.|You want to use my car? You can, of course, but promise me one thing in return: take Honolulu on a nice trip.|Whew... Finally we've arrived at the party. Now, Commander, wait here for thirty minutes while I reapply my makeup. Relax, I'm just joking! Hehehe~
102133.feeling5: As much as I like parties, I like being alone with you even more, Commander... Maybe we could sneak out and go for a drive together? But probably not~ Hehehe~
102133.unlock: Oh my, what a good little commander you've been, waiting here all this time for me. Hop in~ Did you think you would be driving? Hehe, you shouldn't underestimate me~
102133.drop_descrip: Oh my, what a good little commander you've been, waiting here all this time for me. Hop in~ Did you think you would be driving? Hehe, you shouldn't underestimate me~
102133.mission: You have an urgent mission? I'll wait another five minutes for you, then.
102133.home: Do you have everything, Commander? We're not driving back if you forgot to bring something.
102133.mail: Helena messaged me, saying the party's starting soon. Check your mail, then let's hurry on back to the venue.

401460.detail: Z46 is but a codename, not my actual name. For a ship, something like a name should be unimportant, but...
401460.touch: Being able to be touched is proof of one’s existence.
401460.login: This world is so different that from what I was expecting. How interesting!
401460.battle: For not fleeing upon seeing my visage, I applaud both your courage and your stupidity.
401460.hp_warning: What doesn't kill you only makes you stronger.
401460.feeling2: The journey to find a name has lead me to this place.
401460.mission_complete: Freedom and fortune only favor the hardworking.
401460.main: I have experienced neither failure nor suffering. Consequently, I have accomplished nothing.|A name is not merely a label. It is also proof that one exists in this world.|The things I have yet to experience and understand are as numerous as the countless stars in the night sky.
401460.feeling5: To be needed, yearned for, trusted, and loved... "I" am a cloth dyed by your color. My beloved, please bestow a name upon me.
401460.upgrade: Though this is but a trivial thing, I'll return the favor for your consideration.
401460.unlock: Are you the one who summoned me? I am... unfortunately, still without a name. You may call me Z46 for now though.
401460.feeling4: The sea breeze caressing my cheeks, the crashing of waves resounding in my ear. The laughter echoing on the beach, the footprints left in the sand. The rays of summer shimmering overhead, the fluttering sails of ships about to return... What an unforgettable scenery.
401460.feeling1: Perhaps what I seek... cannot be found here.
401460.propose: My beloved, I have long awaited this day. What name have you decided to bestow upon me?
401460.skill: The unworthy are fated to drown in this world.
401460.profile: Iron Blood Z-class destroyer, 1936-C Type. Four other sister ships were planned for construction, but only Z47 and I were built. I wasn’t even completed by the end of the war, and was scrapped without ever being finished. One day, I hope to be called not as Z46, but by a true name.
401460.touch2: If your desire is righteous, then why do your hands tremble?
401460.mission: Unknown beings and new acquaintances... let us sally forth to meet them!
401460.home: Is the battle over, or has it just begun?
401460.win_mvp: Am I too strong? Or are you all too weak?
401460.expedition: Waiting at the harbor for dispatched ships to return... is something I’ve ever experienced before.
401460.mail: Receiving mail is proof of the expectations and trust that people have in you.
401460.feeling3: Friendship, enmity, love, hate... these are things that I have never experienced prior to coming here.
401460.lose: Go and boast to the world. Be proud that you have bested me even once.

502018.touch: Is something the matter, dear? Yat Sen is always there for you. Yes, no matter what.
502018.battle: As long as you're with me, there's nothing that Yat Sen cannot do.
502018.main: For us to walk hand in hand until we become old... is my greatest wish. |I am now able to move forward without doubts... and it's all thanks to you, dear. |I never realized it before, but being by your side like this, watching Ping Hai and Ning Hai grow, and seeing the merriment of the other Dragon Empery children... makes me see that I am truly blessed.
502018.feeling5: Even if we are to be separated, our hearts will always beat as one. Do you feel the same way about me, my dear? Hehe~
502018.unlock: Commander, thank you for waiting for me. Though I am unworthy of this honor, thank you so much...
502018.drop_descrip: Commander, thank you for waiting for me. Though I am unworthy of this honor, thank you so much...
502018.touch2: P-Please don't be so hasty, dear... at least, wait until we get back to our room...
502018.home: Awaiting the return of a loved one... is a warm feeling.

101140.detail: Come on, hurry up. It's exhausting to hold this pose!
101140.touch: C-Commander... Could you stop touching me for a while?! I'm getting sore...
101140.login: It's so annoying having to greet you every day...
101140.battle: You want me to be the flagship? That's too much work...
101140.feeling2: Who would ever be interested in me... You're a real pain in the neck...
101140.mission_complete: *Sigh* Do I really need to remind you every time you need to collect your rewards?
101140.main: *Tsk* Is the food ready yet?|Commander... this doesn't go... oh forget it. It's too much trouble to fix.|Thatcher and Spence are always fighting. Can't they just quiet down?
101140.feeling5: I feel like... I want to help you with stuff... Even though that's a bother... I'm so annoyed...
101140.unlock: *Tsk* Greetings... I hate greetings. But I suppose it's a formality... Hello, Commander. I'm Foote...
101140.feeling4: Isn't it annoying to have to call me over all the time? I think I'll just move into your room instead...
101140.feeling1: *Tsk* Could you just stop bothering me?
101140.propose: This is annoying... But if it's for your sake then I have no choice...
101140.drop_descrip: Fletcher-class destroyer - Foote, Hull Number DD-511!
101140.profile: I'm Foote, one of the Fletcher-class Little Beavers. You think you have family issues? Try remembering the names of your thirty older sisters and nearly a hundred younger sisters...
101140.touch2: Being shy... is also pretty annoying...
101140.mission: Can't you just finish these missions already?
101140.home: Being your secretary is so bothersome... I'm getting tired... Zzz...
101140.win_mvp: You don't need to praise me for something this easy.
101140.expedition: I love not having to go out on commissions... but it's annoying that I have to report back to you every time one of the girls come back...
101140.mail: Mail's here. There, I told you.
101140.feeling3: You're being surprisingly quiet, Commander. I'll keep you company for a while longer then.
101140.lose: *Tsk* Too much trouble. I don't wanna play with these guys anymore.

203089.login: As a royal elite... Ah, um... Welcome back, Commander.
203089.main: Even though I said I had become more mature, there are things that can't be changed overnight... |nil|My clothes won't hang down into the water now, but don't you think this is a bit too revealing...?
203089.unlock: Commander, what do you think? I look more mature than I did before... right?
203089.drop_descrip: Commander, what do you think? I look more mature than I did before... right?
203089.touch2: Eek! Commander... P-please pay attention to the time and place...
203089.home: Good work, Commander. Would you like to take a little break?

401463.detail: Countless days and nights of hard work congeal into a single flash of brilliance onstage. Like a shooting star, leaving only a fleeting trail of light—
401463.touch: My singing voice... is proof of my existence.
401463.login: As long as your eyes are fixed upon me; Upon this stage I shall sing bravely.
401463.battle: In front of tens and thousands of adoring fans... I must do my very best.
401463.main: The star-lit stage is another world of its own, an ajar door to the unknown that now beckons me...|My dear friend, there is no reason to worry about me. All of this was made possible by Z23, Z35, Graf Spee, Admiral Hipper... We are all connected by the bonds of the Iron Blood.|Take heed of where the other performers and your audience are looking? ...I see. I understand why such a thing is important, but can you explain to me why it is called the "Evil Eye?"
401463.feeling5: Anxiety and nervousness gather along with the light upon this stage, and the colors of my heart cannot be concealed... O you who I love, are these feelings reaching you?
401463.unlock: Dancing beams of light, shimmering on-stage; uplifted voices, joined as one by song... Upon this unknown stage, my heart doth flutter... Yet this sensation, is quite refreshing.
401463.drop_descrip: Dancing beams of light, shimmering on-stage; uplifted voices, joined as one by song... Upon this unknown stage, my heart doth flutter... Yet this sensation, is quite refreshing.
401463.home: The stage is yet another battlefield, where wars are fought not with steel and fire, but with our charm and earnest desire.
401463.win_mvp: Let us sing this song of celebration; For our friends' displays of dedication.
401463.expedition: A commission fleet has returned to port. I wish for them to see me as I am now, as a beloved idol.
401463.lose: Have my lessons been so insufficient; or are my emotions simply deficient?

502021.detail: How'd I even get lost...? My map of the local sea should be perfectly accurate...
502021.touch: I'm tired and my muscles hurt... But it was all worth it for that awesome beachside barbeque!
502021.login: *panting*... S-sorry, Commander... I wound up on some weird uninhabited island... *panting*... I swam away for dear life and finally made it back... *panting*...
502021.battle: You're not taking my fried noodles from me!
502021.main: I wanna geh closer to tha firrwurks... Lemme wide on your shouldersh, Commander~! Err... N-no! I'm not drunk!|Come here, Ping Hai. Let me take care of that stain on your lips.|Ping Hai! You can't get careless just because we're not in batt– Blurph!
502021.unlock: Summer's all about the beach! And the beach is all about good food! Let's find something good to eat, Commander.
502021.drop_descrip: Summer's all about the beach! And the beach is all about good food! Let's find something good to eat, Commander.
502021.touch2: Calm down, Commander, I'm trying to watch the fireworks... Your shoulders hurt? Come on, I'm not that heavy!
502021.win_mvp: I want another helping of seafood with fried noodles!

107020.detail: Aww, your frown has curled your brows. You have your share of hard work too, Commander...
107020.touch: Commander, you seem like a hapless little brother~
107020.login: Oh my~ Where are you heading, Commander? Don't worry. As long as I'm around, even the high flying crane won't get away
107020.battle: Everyone! Let's claim victory for our Commander!
107020.hp_warning: Maybe it's time to cheer everyone up with my song~
107020.feeling2: Being an idol is a job that brings smiles to everyone. Of course, that includes you too, Commander. *giggles*
107020.mission_complete: Carrier planes, bring the mission rewards to the Commander
107020.main: I'm not as lively as my younger sister, though I'm confident in my own charms. What do you think~|Oh my, where is Saratoga hiding? She's such a handful...|My eyes are gorgeous? Well, for an idol, my eyes have to look like this~
107020.feeling5: A solo live show? Oh, I haven't had plans for that yet. But if someone were to give me a ring as a present, maybe I'll host that kind of show every day. And the audience is only a single person, you see~
107020.upgrade: *giggles* I suddenly feel like singing. Wanna listen?
107020.unlock: Good day, Mr. Commander~ I am Lexington. I heard that my name was from the first battlefield of the War for Independance. As an idol, I think I need to have a big heart. Don't you agree?
107020.feeling4: Commander, wanna try becoming my manager? You're capable and you know me, and I can't think of you as anything short of dependable~
107020.feeling1: Oh dear, you are mistaken if you think I'm going to accept everything you do.
107020.propose: Oh, oh my oh my~ I was wondering how long I would have to wait for you, Commander~ *giggles* Well then, the private live show ticket has been sold out~ The show goes-- forever~
107020.drop_descrip: Lexington-class aircraft carrier ー Lexington, Hull Number CV-2!
107020.profile:
Oh my~ I am aircraft carrier Lexington. 
I'm gentle? That's because I'm everyone's older sister~ That means you are a cute junior too! 
I feel assured since I've seen Saratoga working hard. Please give some attention to her as well
107020.touch2: Oh goodness, are you unsatisfied with being the younger brother?
107020.mission: Oh Commander, there are still missions that have yet to be completed~
107020.home: Oh, something's on your face. I'll wipe it off, so don't move~
107020.win_mvp: *giggles* Lady Lex is not really a title of mine~
107020.expedition: Oh my~ The girls of the commission team have returned
couple_encourage: Sara, don't be naughty!
Should we get some tea together when this is over?
The Monkey Corps have arrived!
107020.mail: A new mail has arrived. If your hands are full then perhaps I should reply it for you~
107020.feeling3: Recently, whenever I dream about the Coral Sea, you are there, Commander. It somehow makes me feel safe. I wonder why~
107020.lose: Oh my~ we can't keep up with their pace. Should we retreat for now?

201212.detail: Don't worry, guys~! I've already packed all your favorite foods!
201212.touch: Commander, your hands are freezing cold! Jeez, it's payback time! Take this! And this!
201212.battle: Everyone, let's do our best to kick back and relax!
201212.main: Commander, the others are rushing us. Let's finish strong, so we can join them on the beach! |Look at all our friends out there! Commander, if you don't mind, I'll go prepare some extra lunches! |Commander, let's make a bunch of unforgettable memories on the beach this year as well!
201212.unlock: Everyone, hurry up! We rarely get to go out to play, so let's make every minute count! Javelin packed plenty of lunches, so let's have a picnic by the beach!
201212.drop_descrip: Everyone, hurry up! We rarely get to go out to play, so let's make every minute count! Javelin packed plenty of lunches, so let's have a picnic by the beach!
201212.touch2: Commander, if you want to be more popular, you'll have to treat your girls better~

207062.detail: I shall strive to always be your beacon of glory, Commander! ...B-but, that doesn't sound convincing at all while I'm wearing this dress, does it...?
207062.touch: You don't want me catching a cold, is it? I appreciate your concern.
207062.login: Commander, the glory of... the glory of the Royal Navy will...! F-forget it!
207062.main: Are you talking about Ark Royal...? Do you not think that it is appropriate for us adults to monitor the growth of our Destroyer sisters, even off the battlefield?|I bought this outfit because I thought it looked gorgeous, but... then this happened... Wh-what do you mean I can just leave it like this?|The scent of plums wafting upon the evening breeze is so calming... Oh no, I still have to finish my secretary duties!
207062.feeling5: Commander, if you're tired, feel free to rest in my lap. Not only is it ideal for you to replenish your energy, but it is also my duty to provide you succor.
207062.unlock: I heard that the Sakura Empire's traditional attire was really hard to put on... but the Dragon's Empery's outfits are even more... Huh?! Commander, p-please look away!
207062.drop_descrip: I heard that the Sakura Empire's traditional attire was really hard to put on... but the Dragon's Empery's outfits are even more... Huh?! Commander, p-please look away!
207062.touch2: B-but, the glory of the Royal Navy... (blushes)
207062.home: Commander, don't let your guard down... Huh? I'm the one who looks more vulnerable right now?!
207062.win_mvp: To Glorious goes the victory! Commander, thank you for your support!
207062.mail: The hot water is over here... Oh, the mail! Um... I'm so sorry, I could've sworn the mail was right there...
207062.lose: I must gain a better grasp of the situation on the battlefield.

10100061.drop_descrip: It's good to take it easy and celebrate once in a while, but especially in moments like these, you can't afford to let your guard down. Commander, why don't we spar for a bit? Don't even think about holding back - come at me!

401462.detail: I wish to run as fast as a leopard, and fly to great heights like a soaring bird.
401462.touch: Just a small piece of paper... can create such a profound tie between people... this "scavenger hunt" is more interesting than I thought.
401462.main: To compete with others and prove your worth, through different means than fighting battles... To be crowned "champion," 'tis a great feeling. |Even in this little academy, there are so many things to do and see... |Whether your sweat is falling on the track, or your words are encouraging others, all of this is an unforgettable experience.
401462.feeling5: Whatever color you may wish to bestow upon my existence – be it black, red, or blue, I shall accept it all. My beloved, please bestow upon me my name, the identity you choose to bless me with.
401462.unlock: Through the sweat and tears, striving for your goals. Rejoice in victory, sink within defeat... How fascinating, this "sports meet" may be.
401462.drop_descrip: Through the sweat and tears, striving for your goals. Rejoice in victory, sink within defeat... How fascinating, this "sports meet" may be.
401462.touch2: Where are your fingers... Is there really anything worth exploring right there?
401462.home: Steel yourselves for this upcoming battle! Intense fights await, at our next sports meet!

502020.detail: What is it? You want to watch a martial arts performance?
502020.touch: What, you want to have a go with me?
502020.login: Where were you? Lazing around again?! Did you bring me any food...? Hmph. Let's get to work.
502020.battle: I'll never hold back against our enemies!
502020.feeling2: Come on! What's going on with this month's expenses?! Why are these buns here... Have I eaten? Not yet... Fine, let's eat together.
502020.mission_complete: Rewards have been counted. We could buy a huge stack of steamed buns... *ahem* The list is here, Commander.
502020.main: Even if you put a giant plate of steamed buns on the table in front of me, I won't relax...|Commander, I would rather see you and the fleet become stronger instead of just myself. |You cannot protect your loved ones if you neglect your training.
502020.feeling5: There's an old saying in our nation: "It's easy to go from a life of frugality to one of extravagance, but not the other way around." I hope that the one I like would not turn me into a frivolous... wh-wh-why would I say that I like you? You must have heard me wrong.
502020.upgrade: I've got to work even harder to balance the fleet's income and expenses.
502020.unlock: You're the Commander? Well, from this day forward, I'll take the duty of supervising the fleet. I hope you'll coopera... Buns? Thank you, I'll help myself.
502020.feeling4: You won't trick me this time! I'm telling you... Eh? You like me? Wait, th-this must be your new way of tricking me! Uu...
502020.feeling1: As if I'd eat your buns!
502020.propose: ... Since you trust me so much, Commander, why don't we plan ahead? The next focus of our fleet is... cost cutting! We've got to maintain the fleet by minimizing expenses, and... Hey! Don't run away!
502020.drop_descrip: Ning Hai-class Light Cruiser, Ning Hai
502020.skill: I'll show you the power of kung fu!
502020.profile: I'm Ning Hai, the first ship of the Ning Hai-class! In order to revive our nation's navy, we have been living as frugally as possible. If you waste our efforts, Commander, I'm going to be very angry with you!
502020.touch2: *sigh* I won't forgive you, even if you beg God for forgiveness and bribe me with a lifetime supply of steamed buns.
502020.mission: Missions won't complete themselves if you are daydreaming. Let's get going!
502020.home: I just finished steaming these buns. Why not relax and have a quick snack?
502020.win_mvp: Everyone must aspire to outperform me!
502020.expedition: Commander, the prior commission should be finished just about now.
couple_encourage: Ping Hai! Stop eating my buns!
502020.mail: Reading the mail in a timely manner is a common courtesy. Make sure to properly respond as well!
502020.feeling3: Don't always try to change the subject to buns when we're discussing serious business, Commander! Do I look like I can be bought that easily? Ooo... mmm.... So delicious!

203090.detail: Shropshire can be quite a handful to deal with... But, I suppose since she's the type of person who won't ever let herself draw the short straw, you should just let her be.
203090.touch: Commander, your collar is messed up. And your hair too... Hold still, I'll fix it for you.
203090.login: Are you ready to begin working? Don't come running to me if you find out later that you're missing something.
203090.battle: For the sake of not bringing shame upon the fleet, let us fight!
203090.feeling2: The way London always has that smile plastered on her face no matter who she's around just rubs me the wrong way.
203090.mission_complete: So these are the mission rewards! Commander, you're quite the capable one~
203090.main: Excessive kindness can become poison. One must be strict when the situation calls for it. |If you have time to gawk at me, you should get your work done first. After you finish, then you can, um... |... If you're tired, get some rest. I'm not saying this for your sake - it's simply better if you're ready to give it your all when the situation calls for it.
203090.feeling5: At least I'll feel at ease leaving London in your care... No, you'll have to become even more distinguished, to the point that I won't be able to look away from you... huh? What did I just say...?
203090.upgrade: Thank you. I'll continue to work hard on the next mission.
203090.unlock: So you're the Commander? Hmph! Let's make one thing clear: I'm not easygoing like my sister, London. I'll expect you to have your act together!
203090.feeling4: *sigh*... What's more, when I went to bring this up with her, she just gave me a pat on the head and said, "Thanks, Sussex, but it'll be alright." So, nothing changed at all... Good grief, why do people have to be so difficult...?
203090.feeling1: London is too much of a people-pleaser, and all her coddling seems to have turned you into mush.
203090.propose: At first, I was strict with you only because I wanted to ease the burden on my sister... but gradually, I began to hope that you would become the most distinguished person in my life... As of now, you've already become that person...
203090.profile: Other than the coastal defence battle in the Mediterranean Sea and that one naval battle up north, I pretty much carried out all my missions normally... Well, there was that one time I needed serious repairs... b-but anyway! Since I'm here, I'll continue to put my best foot forward. Commander, I expect the same from you!
203090.touch2: Commander, sit right there! Good grief... I'll have to re-teach you some basic manners...!
203090.mission: Before acting, one must first consider the most efficient way of getting things done - you haven't forgotten, right?
203090.home: There's a lot to report still, but for now, good work.
203090.win_mvp: Don't think that winning is the only thing that matters. There are still many things I could have done better.
203090.expedition: And that should be time... Commander, the commission team should be returning any moment now.
couple_encourage: London, stay safe out there!
Shropshire, stay focused on the battlefield!
203090.mail: Please do not forget to check your mail.
203090.feeling3: London is the type of person who would easily be deceived by a bad person, but still continue to smile despite knowing that... Jeez, just why does she have to have that kind of personality...
203090.lose: This was due to my failure as a leader. Don't blame yourselves, everyone.

10100051.drop_descrip: Oh, Commander? Won't you join me in a short conversation? I'll tell you things about Planeptune. Oh, and I'm eagerly awaiting the day you come to Planeptune for a visit.

303170.detail: Commander? Oh, I'm just preparing for the next lecture at the auditorium. Please don't worry about me, and continue your work as normal.
303170.touch: Commander... where do you think you're looking? Don't think I wouldn't notice... I could feel your gaze boring into me... Am I right?
303170.login: Welcome back, Commander. Which job should we take on first?
303170.battle: I won't run away again... I swear it!
303170.hp_warning: As if this... would be enough to make me turn back!
303170.feeling2: Would you like to learn more about the Mogami class? Very well, I'll be glad to explain everything from the top. Which one of us would you like to hear about first?
303170.mission_complete: The mission rewards have arrived. That is good news.
303170.main: Commander is looking at... N-nothing, don't worry about it!|Kumano, please don't make trouble for Mogami, all right? She's going to get a stomachache again...|We're sometimes called the Suzuya class, but I still prefer being called the Mogami class. We all fought together during that war after all..
303170.feeling5: Ahh... Commander, your gaze is so passionate... so I can finally tell you... I've always admired you... Huh?! What's this? I feel all fluttery...!
303170.upgrade: My abilities have been enhanced. Well done.
303170.unlock: I am Suzuya, Mogami-class heavy cruiser. I place myself under your command from this day forward.
303170.feeling4: ...There's no point hiding it. I already know how you feel about me. Just shut up and... give in to your feelings already!
303170.feeling1: Mogami may often fail to recognize her own worth, but more and more people are starting to see how little you're worth.
303170.propose: (whispers) Commander, when this ritual is over... you know what's next, right? Don't worry. I'll treat you better than anyone else. Isn't that right, darling~♡
303170.drop_descrip: Mogami-class heavy cruiser number three – Suzuya.
303170.profile: I am Suzuya, third ship of the Mogami class. During that war, I fought alongside Mogami as a member of CruDiv 7. My last battle left me with a bit of regret... but I've been given a new beginning on this battlefield, and I'll fight alongside my new companions with a fresh outlook. I look forward to working with you.
303170.touch2: Nnh... So this is what you were after from the very beginning... I knew it all along. I've always known, this entire time... Ehehehe~♡
303170.mission: I've arranged the status of our current missions. Please look over them.
303170.home: We must apply what we've learned to future battles. Shall I prioritize writing the report first?
303170.win_mvp: Congratulations. Eh, I'm the MVP...? Th-thank you very much...
303170.expedition: The commission team has returned to port. What's next? Shall I go with you to greet them?
couple_encourage: I can understand your pain.
Did I also...? No, I would never.
303170.mail: The mail has arrived. There's something for you, Commander... Ah...
303170.feeling3: You're... most interested in Suzuya? Of course, I'd be glad to give you the details... but just explaining things wouldn't be enough, right...?

702010.detail: For combat to be the sole purpose of my existence is a strange and novel feeling.
702010.login: Ah, Commander, you're back! Would you like some borscht?
702010.feeling2: Commander, care for a drink? Whether you can get me to do strange things afterwards... depends entirely on your ability~
702010.main: I have a big heart? Thanks for the compliment. |As the herald of dawn, I shall bring light to everyone.|Bears? They’re pretty cute. I used to raise one.
702010.feeling5: Я люблю тебя, Commander. If you want to know what it means, you'll have to learn my mother tongue... and come to my hometown.
702010.upgrade: I feel like I could lift an entire bear! Hehe...
702010.unlock: Здравствуйте! Avrora, reporting in. Along with the light of dawn, I shall bring you victory.
702010.feeling4: Commander, everyone from my hometown is straightforward, and I'm no exception... If you can finish this drink, you can do anything you'd like with me...
702010.feeling1: Even I am unable to shed a light into the darkness of your heart, Commander?
702010.propose: Commander, are you all geared up? The journey is going to be cold. Don't worry! I've brought plenty of vodka to keep us warm...
702010.skill: Within the light of dawn are spilled blood and raging flames...
702010.profile: I am Avrora, a light cruiser. I started a famous revolution, but I cannot understand what happened to the world after that...|I’m no more than just another soldier in your fleet. Please utilize my abilities to their fullest, and I’ll make sure to ring victory to the fleet.
702010.touch2: You should express your feelings in a more passionate manner.
702010.mission: A new mission! I'm more excited than I should be.
702010.home: Good work, Commander. Would you like a bottle of vodka to warm you up?
702010.win_mvp: We must remember the sacrifices that made this victory possible...
702010.expedition: Commander, a commission has been completed. Let’s bring some vodka to the girls to warm them up.
couple_encourage: Gangut, don't bully the commander too much, okay?
Kuku? I'm not sure I want to call you that... Ahaha...
Forward, comrades of the Northern Parliament!
702010.mail: This mail has traveled a long way to get here. Please read it.
702010.feeling3: My hometown? It’s very beautiful. Although if you want to go there, you would need to be prepared for the cold. Me? I’ll be fine, even without clothes. Hehe... want proof?
702010.lose: The Revolution shall not cease its march.

207061.detail: You're saying... that failures are just learning opportunities? Thanks, Commander, I do feel a lot better now.
207061.login: When I put on this uniform, my mood seems to lighten up compared to usual...
207061.main: Commander, Ardent told me about some fascinating places. Want to go check them out after the operation is over? |Commander, what would you consider an ideal school life? |Even though I still have much to learn... I swear to bring you true glory one day, Commander.
207061.unlock: Being able to occasionally have a peaceful school life... is something I could get used to. Commander, look at the markings on this butterfly - aren't they lovely?
207061.drop_descrip: Being able to occasionally have a peaceful school life... is something I could get used to. Commander, look at the markings on this butterfly - aren't they lovely?
207061.touch2: Hey!! Commander, you scared the butterfly away...
207061.home: Commander, remember to not let your guard down on your way home.

317010.detail: There's only so many things a regular submarine can do. To turn the war around, we need more wings in the air.
317010.touch: I'm okay with lending you my Seiran, but it's veeeeery expensive! Break it, and I'll be really angry, okay?
317010.login: Welcome back, Commander. The skies are ever blue!
317010.battle: Let's give it our best shot.
317010.hp_warning: I guess this is all a submarine can do...
317010.feeling2: Welcome to my room, Commander. I've got books on aircraft lying around if you want to read those. Oh, and please be careful around the model plane on the shelf over there.
317010.mission_complete: Commander, my Seiran just came back with the mission rewards.
317010.main: Don't get the wrong idea about me, Commander. I do love aircraft, but that doesn't mean I hate myself for being a submarine.|The sea is the color of the sky. And the sky is the same color as me!|There's the Type 97 and Type 99, the Suisei, Tenzan, Ryuusei, Saiun, and of course, my Seiran. I know everything there is to know about aircraft!
317010.feeling5: I want to repay you somehow for everything you've done for me, Commander. I'll do anything you want! If I can help you, you can then help me back.
317010.upgrade: Maybe I can fit a few more Seirans once I get stronger?
317010.unlock: Hi, Commander. I'm the aviation submarine I-13. My hobbies include aircraft and gazing up at the sky! Also, this is my friend, my Seiran. I'm glad to meet you.
317010.feeling4: I've gotten closer to the carrier's aircraft now, and it's all thanks to you. I've never been this happy before in my life. Thank you, Commander!
317010.feeling1: You just don't understand me either, do you, Commander?
317010.propose: A... Hellcat? An Avenger? Even a Hurricane, and all these other planes?! You... went out and borrowed them all just for me? Oh, Commander... I love you so much I can't even think straight...!
317010.drop_descrip: Type A Mod. 2 cruiser submarine – I-13.
317010.skill: Here it comes... Everything I'm capable of!
317010.profile: I'm I-13, formally known as the Type A Mod. 2 cruiser submarine model thirteen. Some people call me the fifth of the Type A model, but I was really just an upgraded model that could store Seirans. Sounds cool, doesn't it? Well, sadly, I didn't achieve much of note...
317010.touch2: Don't make me pepper you with my Seiran's machine guns.
317010.mission: Remember to give those missions a look, okay, Commander?
317010.home: Nice job on that last mission, Commander.
317010.win_mvp: This victory will be a great help to our other fleets.
317010.expedition: Hey, Commander, a commission should be done by now.
317010.mail: Commander, my Seiran has arrived with mail.
317010.feeling3: You think I'm weird, do you? Heheh, maybe I am... Just remember: there are only so many things a regular submarine can do. That's something I learned during my short time in service.
317010.lose: It's not good enough to be an ordinary submarine...

401464.touch: Allow me to complete this seal, and it may be of great use to you.
401464.login: I eagerly await the completion of this next piece... It's as if my soul resonates with this craft.
401464.main: The festival to herald the arrival of spring is sanguine, filled with joy, fanfare, and deliciousness. None may resist its delights.|Sister of my friend, please wait a bit longer. The preparation process is difficult to control.|After this piece is complete, will you mount it? The more delicate the art, the more strict the protection must be...
401464.unlock: "Jianzhi," the art of breathing life into works of cut paper... is a world beyond my imagination. If these decorations are said to usher in blessings... are they akin to a coat-of-arms or a holy seal?
401464.drop_descrip: "Jianzhi," the art of breathing life into works of cut paper... is a world beyond my imagination. If these decorations are said to usher in blessings... are they akin to a coat-of-arms or a holy seal?
401464.touch2: Are you trying to stick something onto me?
401464.home: I have no desire to be a burden upon my peers... Before devoting myself to this craft, I shall continue to observe.

801010.detail: If you have any questions, feel free to ask away. I will respond to each one.
801010.touch: Commander, you'll be missing out if you treat me and my sisters as regular destroyers.
801010.login: My, I see you've returned? What shall your orders be today? I am ready to accept any assignment - commission or sortie!
801010.battle: In the name of Iris Libre, let us break their lines!
801010.hp_warning: The outcome... still isn't set in stone!
801010.feeling2: Don't you think Noblesse Oblige is an elegant idea?
801010.mission_complete: Commander, here are the fruits of your labor.
801010.main: My sword and shield? Oh, they stop feeling heavy after a while. Well, I also am quite strong. |If I was with my sisters at that time... would things have happened differently...?|Whether someone is friend or foe... is not something set in stone.
801010.feeling5: Commander, as long as we're together, I feel like I can easily overcome any adversity... that's what I truly believe.
801010.upgrade: I feel strength rippling from my sword and shield... Commander, thank you.
801010.unlock: Oh my, Commander, what a pleasure it is to meet you. I am Le Triomphant, an elegant large destroyer from Iris Libre, yours to command. The power of the Le Fantasque-class shall exceed your wildest fantasies.
801010.feeling4: Familiarity with hardship and suffering cultivates an appreciation of life and death. At least that's what I think...
801010.feeling1: So... I guess this is the kind of person that you are, Commander...
801010.propose: Finally... this day has come at last... Commander, you truly are my fated partner. I, Le Triomphant, willingly offer you my sword, my shield, and my body.
801010.profile: I am Le Triomphant, a Le Fantasque-class Destroyer from Iris Libre. It is an honor to meet you. My sisters and I were in the 8th Light Division before the fateful Battle of Jutland. After that, our paths diverged...
801010.touch2: Eek! To think that you're even faster than the Le Fantasque class... you're not one to be taken lightly, Commander.
801010.home: That was a hard-fought battle, Commander. Would you like to have a cup of tea before you resume work?
801010.win_mvp: You'll find that the speed of the Le Fantasque-class is not easily matched!
801010.expedition: Why don't you let me handle the next one? I'll get it done the fastest.
couple_encourage: Let us dedicate this victory to Commander!
801010.mail: It feels nice to be celebrated by someone you don't know, doesn't it?
801010.feeling3: In order to realize their ideals and ambitions, even family members may part ways and eventually meet each other on the battlefield... It's so tragic...
801010.lose: Sometimes... things like this can happen as well...

701020.detail: Lifting my lovely кролик really does make comrade Commander behave. Just as Chapayev said.
701020.touch: Comrade Commander, is this snack my reward for my hard labor...?
701020.login: *burp*... Hello, comrade Commander. You followed my scent? Then how about a drink?
701020.battle: I dunno what to say. Let's go with... Ураааа!
701020.hp_warning: I haven't had enough to drink...
701020.feeling2: Everyone tells me that is getting food from strange people is one thing, but making strangers *into* food is not okay.
701020.mission_complete: Well done, comrade Commander. Now we have all the ingredients for tonight's soup.
701020.main: *burp*... Say, comrade Commander, do you know anyone else who drinks this? One with bunny ears? Interesting...|Those "Four Unbreakables" are a cool bunch. I wish I could join them, but that's not possible 'cause that would ruin the naming convention. Very unfortunate.|I don't like foxes or invaders, 'cause they both try to take my home from me. Once they show up, you must drive them away.
701020.feeling5: *burp*... We've drunk all there is, comrade Commander. It feels like my drinks taste better when we enjoy them together. Let's have some more another time... *yawn*... But now, I need some sleep...
701020.upgrade: I much prefer the Northern Parliament's drinks! *burp*!
701020.unlock: здра́вствуйте, comrade Commander. I am Gnevny-class destroyer Grozny, reporting for duty... What is the matter, comrade Commander? The item in my right hand? This is my lovely кролик. It's a cute убийца.
701020.feeling4: It's not decent to ask you to share your food all the time, comrade Commander. That's why I'm going to start sharing mine with you. Here, want a drink?
701020.feeling1: You're strange, comrade Commander. Everyone tells me not to talk to strange people, but wouldn't you be lonely then...?
701020.propose: I think I like me a drink more than a ring. Here, drink this, and we'll become family, comrade Commander. Hm? You might be right; aren't we already like family...?
701020.profile: I am Gnevny-class destroyer Grozny. I was part of convoys, laid mines, and provided shore firing support at one point. Call for me if you have orders, comrade Commander. And if you'll let me indulge in some drinks, I'll be delighted.
701020.touch2: кролик bites when it gets angry. Well, not so much bite as slice... I guess.
701020.mission: "She who does not work, neither shall she eat," seems to be the rule here. With that in mind, we should finish these missions now so we may drink tomorrow.
701020.home: Comrade Commander, want some borscht and hot cocoa?
701020.win_mvp: хорошо. Now I'm getting warmed up... Huh? It's over already?
701020.expedition: Comrade Commander, I will go to the pier ahead of you. I'm eager to meet everyone who's returned.
couple_encourage: Are you a bunny? That's cute.
701020.mail: There's nothing odd about me delivering your mail, comrade Commander. We all take turns doing it, after all.
701020.feeling3: Always I get told to stay away from strange people, but you're not strange, comrade Commander. Meaning it should be fine to accept food from you.
701020.lose: Blahh... I've had a few drinks too many...

306091.detail: Heehee... Commander, take this! A direct hit from my water gun! Oh, you got some saltwater in your mouth? I'm terribly sorry... So, Commander... tell me, how did it taste? Hahaha~
306091.touch: The glamorous Chiyoda in a swimsuit~! No matter how breathtaking I might look, don't just stand there and stare like an idiot. C'mon, let's go and play~
306091.login: Since we're here anyway, we've gotta enjoy the day to the fullest! We can start by playing with some balls. Catch, Commander!
306091.main: Hmm, beach volleyball? ... I'll use my powers to turn Saratoga into a holey woman! Ain't that right, Chitose?|The summer sun, the sparkling sea... Stop lazing around and come play with me already, Chitose~|Oh, Yamashiro and her sister came too. Wouldn't it be a good idea to team up with them? Well?
306091.unlock: Hehe~ If you don't have any other plans, then your only task... is to enjoy a holiday by the sea! Commander, have you switched into vacation mode yet?
306091.drop_descrip: Hehe~ If you don't have any other plans, then your only task... is to enjoy a holiday by the sea! Commander, have you switched into vacation mode yet?
306091.touch2: If you're looking for something nice and round, I can throw this ball at your face, you know...?
306091.home: It's not like I was aiming for your face, you know? My hand just happened to slip, and the ball just happened to make contact with your face... C'mon, get over it. It's just an inflatable ball anyway!

201214.detail: ♪~What kind of lunch should I pack today~
201214.login: Welcome back, Commander! Don't I look super cool today? Ehehe~♪
201214.main: Little Bel and Belfast somehow feel like... mother and child?|Which club should I join...? Cooking club? Knitting club? Nnnh... I just can't decide!|Juneau, are you going shopping with the others later? Aww, let me come too!
201214.touch2: Jeez, no lewding! How many times do I have to repeat myself?
201214.home: Good job out there! Hey, Zed! Save the report for later, and let Commander rest first~!

306090.detail: I help Chitose out with her Shinto duties sometimes. You know, as a shrine maiden. ...Huh? You think I'd be more of a hindrance...?
306090.touch: Am I so beautiful that I caught your eye? I'm flattered, but you should focus on your work for now~
306090.login: Today's another great day to show off my amazing prowess! Commander, let's get pumped!
306090.battle: Let's kick some fine enemy butt on this wonderful day!
306090.feeling2: I went to give Chitose some red bean jellies, but I ended up getting spoiled senseless by her instead... Oh, here's some for you. Please go ahead and try some.
306090.headtouch: Hehehe~ Commander, do you prefer them long or short?
306090.mission_complete: You took care of the missions? Alright. While you take a break, I'm going to go check up on how Chitose's doing.
306090.main: Taaake that! ...Hmm? No reaction... Commander, sometimes you're so much like Chitose, it's honestly quite a letdown...|Doesn't Chitose have really silky hair that smells just divine? Actually, I'm the one who takes care of it everyday.|Whenever we rehearse the dance with Yamashiro and Fusou, some kind of trouble always occurs... Like something falling, or flying off somewhere. But really? I find it find it all to be pretty funny!
306090.feeling5: Y-yeah, I, I guess I've gotten pretty close to you... What would Chitose say if she saw you pampering me like this? Hm... If she saw us like this, she'd probably say, "I love both of you, so it's fine." or something. Yeah, she'd definitely say something like that! Hahaha!
306090.upgrade: Oooh~ I really want to show the new and improved Chiyoda off to Chitose♡
306090.unlock: Hehe, looks like I've kept you waiting! I am the renowned seaplane carrier– err, I mean, aircraft carrier, Chiyoda! In any case, I'll be staying here! Right, right, is my sister Chitose here as well?
306090.feeling4: Oh, the things I'd do for a lap pillow from Chitose right now♡. Seeing she isn't around right now, I guess I'll need a temporary replacement... Hm, maybe the Commander who's slacking off right now. Hey, if you don't want the others to find out you're slacking off, give up your lap to me~ Hehehe... Mmn~
306090.feeling1: Commander. Get away from Chitose. As far as you possibly can.
306090.propose: Now that you've given me this, you're going to be stuck pampering me senseless! You already are? I-I guess that's true... Well, feel free to request whatever you want from me in exchange!
306090.profile: Even though Chitose and I were seaplane tenders, after a loss in a certain battle, we were both remodeled into aircraft carriers. ...Even so, neither of us were able to be of much use until the end... Ahahaha....
306090.touch2: Yikes?! If you had done this to Chitose instead, she'd have turned bright red from embarrassment!
306090.mission: You know, I think it's better to take care of missions as they come in. Yes?
306090.home: Looks like you didn't run into any trouble while I was gone. Hehe, it must be thanks to the protective charm I slipped inside your clothes~
306090.win_mvp: Did you see that? Did you see how amazing I was?
306090.expedition: Commander, the Commissions Team is back.
couple_encourage: Big sis♪ Let's kick some fine enemy butt on this wonderful day☆
306090.mail: There's a letter addressed to you, Commander.
306090.feeling3: Commander, don't you want to try touching Chitose's hair too? Even though she prefers to keep her distance from others, if you ask, she absolutely won't be able to turn you down.
306090.lose: Ugh... I want to bury my face in Chitose's jugs...

301189.detail: My will-o'-wisps burn stronger than before... *Giggle*, this is the power of money... I'm merely jesting, of course.
301189.touch: Yes, yes, your wish has been heard. Please make your way yonder to amuse yourself with my will-o'-wisps.
301189.main: Commander, you can make up for quality with quantity. Believe in yourself and pursue your dreams...|Work diligently and you will only be a fool by your appearance.|I take my work both as a secretary and shopkeeper seriously... If I feel like it... I could offer you a 5% discount.
301189.unlock: If you have this much money remaining... then you may visit me and spend it with confidence... A discount, you say...? Of course... Someday, I shall give you one...
301189.drop_descrip: If you have this much money remaining... then you may visit me and spend it with confidence... A discount, you say...? Of course... Someday, I shall give you one...
301189.touch2: Groping a shopkeeper like this... is surely not a turn-on of yours...?
301189.home: Gawking won't earn you a... *Groan*... Then just for beverages, I could give you... F-fifty percent off.
couple_encourage: What say you we collect parts together?

203092.detail: Miss Renown, do please let the Maids handle banquet security... the Commander is already here Honestly, how are we supposed to start the party without you?!
203092.touch: Commander, look how crooked this is. You really must pay more attention to your formalwear... Right, there we are.
203092.login: How is your work coming along? Keep faffing about like that and you'll be putting in overtime!
203092.battle: The Royal Navy will prevail! Onwards!
203092.main: That Ajax, she's going to do that to the Commander again... I have to do something about her... Ah, it's nothing!|How long are you going to stare at me like that? Don't you have anything better to do?|My sister London is here... Phew, looks like I don't need to worry. I mean, it's London, there was never anything to worry about in the first place.
203092.feeling5: "If you want a d-drink, you can enjoy it like this..." That Ajax, how could she do something so wasteful...? I... What am I doing...?! Commander...?!
203092.unlock: What are you staring at me for? I'm just the same as any of the others... Y-you have a few more hands to shake? Of course...
203092.drop_descrip: What are you staring at me for? I'm just the same as any of the others... Y-you have a few more hands to shake? Of course...
203092.home: N-now that we're through with battle, perhaps we could relax a... No, we have to focus on the party for now!

302129.detail: Yeah? Oh, I'm working on my sortie pose. When goin' to war, you need a war pose, y'know?
302129.login: You're back, huh? Focus on your work. Gimme a shout when it's time to sortie.
302129.battle: Sorry to say, but this is where you'll all die!
302129.hp_warning: Sorry to say... but I can't afford to be defeated here!
302129.main: Violence is the only solution I know of for my problems. That's why I envy you and Jintsuu sometimes.|Whenever I try to be like Jintsuu and use logic to solve problems, I usually end up using my fists anyway. I dunno why, either...|Hardships don't get under my skin, but I'm scared that I'll one day lose my way...
302129.unlock: Hmh. Guess I won't be needin' these bandages anymore. Commander, how about we find out how strong I've gotten... by having you take one of my punches?
302129.drop_descrip: Hmh. Guess I won't be needin' these bandages anymore. Commander, how about we find out how strong I've gotten... by having you take one of my punches?
302129.touch2: Hold still, Commander. We're pals, so I'll only hit you with 80% of my full strength!
302129.home: Nice work. Want some sweets? You can have some of mine. They're all stuff I personally like, though.
302129.win_mvp: Where'd I put my bandages... Oh, right, don't need 'em anymore... Totally forgot.

502010.detail: Is there anything else you would like to know about me, Commander?
502010.touch: What's wrong? Please don't have any strange expectations of me.
502010.login: We meet again, Commander. Do not worry, I shall stay by your side as promised.
502010.battle: Ancestors... Yat Sen shall now do her part as well.
502010.hp_warning: I have already witnessed true hell.
502010.headtouch: I am no longer the crybaby that I once was.
502010.mission_complete: Mission rewards counted and ready for your review... me? No, there's nothing I want...
502010.main: Ning Hai's steamed buns? Mm... they still have the same nostalgic flavor.|Only by remembering the lessons of the past can we move towards a brighter future.|Sometimes, I miss those days when I used to train together with all my sisters...
502010.feeling5: When I look at your face, I sometimes forget to breathe... What a strange sensation.
502010.upgrade: If only I was able to become this strong sooner, then perhaps...
502010.unlock: This is the moment I have long waited for... I am Yat Sen, from the First Fleet of the Dragon Empery. Please allow me to be at your service once more.
502010.feeling4: My past? Those... are stories for your ears only, Commander.
502010.feeling1: Commander... You don't seem to be the one I've been waiting for...
502010.propose: This... is the power of our bond? Every moment we are together is like a dream, one that I am afraid of waking up from. No... it is no matter. From now on, I shall always be by your side.
502010.profile: Yat Sen of the First Fleet of the Dragon Empery, reporting in. I heard that my sisters have already arrived. This time, I promise that I will not leave your side.
502010.touch2: To do such a thing to a woman... Surely Commander is prepared to suffer the consequences.
502010.mission: New missions have been assigned! I have finished preparations and am awaiting your orders.
502010.home: Ahh, home is such a warm place.
502010.win_mvp: As the wind blows anew, I can feel my presence once more.
502010.expedition: The girls have already returned from commission. Aren't we going to greet them?
couple_encourage: I'm so glad I can be with everyone again, just as before.
502010.mail: The mail? It's on your desk, Commander.
502010.feeling3: I am overjoyed to be able to return to your side once more, Commander.
502010.lose: Give up? Why would I do that? I am not the same fragile Yat Sen as before.

401190.login: Commander, skipping breakfast is bad for your body. I've prepared some cereal and toast for you; if you don't mind, would you like to eat together?
401190.battle: All ships, at the ready! Aim for the enemy fleet ahead! Feuer!
401190.feeling2: No matter what skill you have, I'm sure there's a place for it.
401190.mission_complete: Commander, the missions were done perfectly this time! Full marks!
401190.main: I must be more strict with myself now that I'm your secretary.|Commander, if you're free, would you like to play with me?|Commander, I prepared some watermelon for you. Open your mouth~ aah~
401190.feeling5: *yawns* Commander, why haven't you gone back to your room yet? You're sorry for waking me up? No, it's okay... but I only have this single bed here... You want to see how long my fingers are? Why not turn on the lights... Fuehhh?!
401190.upgrade: Am I one step closer to being an adult?
401190.unlock: Z19 Hermann Künne, reporting for duty! Commander, I'm prepared to fight until the very end!
401190.feeling4: Commander, as long as I can see you, my mind is at ease even if you aren't doing anything in particular. Is this what it means to be reliant?
401190.propose: Can I really have this? Thank you very much... I'll do my best to be a worthy partner!
401190.skill: This is the result of all my hard work!
401190.profile: I am the Iron Blood Navy's Z-class 1936-Type destroyer, Hermann Künne.  I participated in Operation Weserübung, and met my end during the fierce engagements at Narvik. Things will be different this time around!
401190.touch2: Please don't pick me up... I'm way too old for that...
401190.mission: Ah, it's already time to get back to work. Commander, let's go complete some missions.
401190.home: Could you play with me for a while, Commander? Oh.. you're tired? I guess rest is pretty important too...
401190.win_mvp: Z23! This time, I got a perfect score!
401190.expedition: Is it finally time for you to play with me?
401190.mail: There's new mail, Commander. Surely there's a commendation from the higher-ups!
401190.feeling3: Commander, if I get MVP in the next battle, would you take me to a water park on your next day off?
401190.lose: Ugh... Mission... failed. Commander, I'm terribly sorry.

702020.detail: Believe it or not, but I'm from the same era as Avrora and Mikasa! So, you know what you oughta do as the commander here, don'tcha?
702020.touch: Ah, "getting personal," are we? Hehehe~ Where do you wanna touch me, huh~?
702020.login: Yoohoo, Commander! What task are we starting today with?
702020.battle: I'm ready to ram! Let's gooooo!
702020.feeling2: This isn't a naval cabin, so why is my room so plain? If I'm to actually live here, you'll need to get some much better interior decor!
702020.headtouch: What are you doing? Didn't Mikasa teach you to respect girls with rich histories?
702020.mission_complete: Mission complete! Haha! I did my share of work, so I'm gonna claim my reward!
702020.main: Avrora, could you go buy me a new game? Hmm, fine... Then how about the Commander instead? What do you say to that, Commander~?|Secretary work, eh... Like, I'm happy to work hard for you and all, but wouldn't it make you even happier to work hard for me?|It's embarrassing how I'm staring at you constantly? Well, I don't feel embarrassed, so who cares~ Hahah!
702020.feeling5: Sadly for you, I don't belong to anyone, so you don't get to have me♪ But, if you really, *really* insist, theeen... Hehehe, you get what I'm trying to say, don'tcha?
702020.upgrade: I have design limitations, so don't work me like an ox, alright?
702020.unlock: Yoohoo, Commander! I'm *the* Pamiat Merkuria, light cruiser from the Northern Parliament! Nice meeting you! Do your thing and work your butt off for me♪
702020.feeling4: I toss like crazy in my sleep?! Wh-wh-what're you saying?! Were you watching the whole time?! Oh geez, now I'll never be able to get hitched... Now it's your responsibility, Commander♪
702020.propose: Hahaha♪ You're giving me a ring, just like that? Just how thirsty are you, Commander? Next time, think it through first. Whatevs, I'm not gonna make you regret your choice♡
702020.profile: I'm Pamiat Merkuria, protected cruiser. I was a bigshot in the Black Sea Fleet during the great war, beating up baddies left and right, and I even fought alongside Avrora in a world war! I'm charismatic, experienced, and cute - all the things YOU aren't!
702020.touch2: You really like 'em... *big*, huh? You creep♡
702020.mission: You've got missions. Get 'em done. Me? I've got my hands full with this game.
702020.home: You're back, huh? Then get me something to eat, now! I want some of that "ramen" the Sakura Empire's got!
702020.win_mvp: Loooosers! Are you that much weaker than me? Or am I just really strong?
702020.expedition: A commission's been completed! Now gimme your thanks for notifying you!
couple_encourage: What do you mean "nothing's changed"? Hmph!
702020.mail: I'm on letter-giving duty today. You'd *better* appreciate my work♪
702020.feeling3: *yaaawn*... What's this? Bedsheets and a soft pillow? Wow, how thoughtful of you! Now I can get myself a good nap! Right then... *yawn*... Zzz...
702020.lose: Сожаление... And here I thought this fleet was stronger than this...

106029.touch: Yes! Thanks for getting my ball!
106029.main: My goal is the Major Le... I mean, submarine fighting, a three strike finish!|Rest assured, Commander! While I'm doing escort duty, no ships sink under my watch!|I am here today because of Yorkie and Lady Lex. I have to give them my thanks!
106029.unlock: Commander, there's no need to be so afraid. There are only two things my balls hit-- Enemies, and victory! Ah, sometimes they do hit the windows too, ahaha...
106029.drop_descrip: Commander, there's no need to be so afraid. There are only two things my balls hit-- Enemies, and victory! Ah, sometimes they do hit the windows too, ahaha...
106029.touch2: Haha, I'm used to this type of interference now!

207050.detail: ?! ... Ah, I was just doing a bit of tidying up. Please, come right in.
207050.touch: I must admit, Tirpitz is quite the hard nut to crack.
207050.battle: Ladies of the Royal Navy have many virtues, but mercy to enemies is not one of them!
207050.hp_warning: You are all to redouble your efforts!
207050.feeling2: Commander, is there something required of me? If you have a moment, why not join me for a cup of tea?
207050.mission_complete: Commander, please don't forget to review the list of mission rewards.
207050.main: Commander, if you're not making any progress on your work, why not take a break? I've prepared tea and crumpets.|No harm in taking a rest while the Commander's dist– Heavens! Victorious! G-good day. Do you have some business with the Commander?|On the day of my launch, hmm... What a shame... though I didn't do it on purpose... Well! All water under the bridge now, isn't it?
207050.feeling5: Commander, good day to you ♪ Shall we share another cake today? The maids have prepared a dreadfully sweet treat for us! Hmm...? I decided to let my hair down a bit more for you, Commander. Hehehe, I wonder if you'll find me just as captivating a Formidable as I was before?
207050.unlock: Good day, Commander. I am Formidable, third ship of the Illustrious class. Pleased to make your acquaintance.
207050.feeling4: Truthfully, even though I'm a Lady of the Royal Navy, I sometimes want to have a bit of fun too. A side of me that I can't normally show except to people close to me like Illustrious... Doesn't that make you want to get closer with me?
207050.feeling1: I'm afraid I've contracted a disease that gives me a dreadful headache when you're nearby. Would you mind going someplace else?
207050.propose: I, Formidable, hereby dedicate my life to the love of my Commander, through good times and bad, rich times and poor... This is quite long, so I'll omit the rest~ Now then, Commander, it's your turn. I know it's a long vow but you are not to skip a single word ♪
207050.profile: I am Formidable, third ship of the Illustrious class. I operated in the Mediterranean for a time, crossing swords with a certain Veneto. Thereafter, I found myself all across the Seven Seas. While my service record is not particularly impressive, I feel I made a small contribution to the war effort.
207050.touch2: Commander, is this the appropriate way for one to behave?
207050.mission: Commander, please don't forget to review the mission list I prepared for you.
207050.home: Hmm~♪ Hmm~♪ C-Commander! I am p-pleased that you have returned!
207050.win_mvp: What a magnificent victory! Let us press the advantage.
207050.expedition: Commander, the commission is complete. Shall we go to the harbour and greet the team?
couple_encourage: Illustrious, my dear sister, what would you say to a spot of tea after this?
Victorious, my dear sister, have I comported myself well today?
207050.mail: Commander, I'm leaving the mail right here. Please don't forget to review it.
207050.feeling3: My big sisters Illustrious and Victorious, like so many other ships you've gathered here, vouch for what a great commander you are. Now come, let this cake be a symbol of our new friendship. Take a bite, won't you?
207050.lose: Why you miserab- Ahem! You are truly worthy adversaries, but next time victory will be mine!

202100.detail: If you have the time to gape at working maids, you have the time to do your own work. Master.
202100.touch: Do you need something of me? As your maid, Master, I will do what I can to satisfy your requests above and beyond our typical responsibilities.
202100.login: Punctuality is not a virtue, it is rather a duty. Master, do bear that in mind.
202100.battle: Please check your remaining ammunition stocks.
202100.hp_warning: This is not going according... to plan!
202100.feeling2: Everyone makes mistakes. But I will use my experience to reduce the opportunities my master has to make such mistakes. Do be aware.
202100.mission_complete: You have uncollected mission rewards. If you would rather I collect them for you, simply direct me to do so.
202100.main: More trouble from the Royal Maids today... Belfast, do look after this troop of clumsy louts.|That Fiji is always buying cosmetics, clothes and the like... You must not learn from her, Master. Life is to be lived in moderation.|A maid has a maid's work, the master has the master's. The maids serve the master, while the master serves everyone. This is the way of the world.
202100.feeling5: Master, we must improve your daily habits if we are to raise your work efficiency... If you would like, Master, I could take care of- Rather, I would be happy to stay with you.
202100.upgrade: Excellent choice. Now, if you could also strengthen some of the other girls as well, I'd be delighted.
202100.unlock: Gloucester, light cruiser of the Royal Maids, at your service, Master. It is my honor and my duty to assist you in becoming a most magnificent commander.
202100.feeling4: Master, you must be mindful of your comportment around women, particularly the way you touch and handle them... If you find this challenging, I am willing to practice with you. Ahem, now then...
202100.feeling1: I do not speak to things.
202100.propose: Master, you need not resort to such methods to keep me by your side... But if this is indeed your wish, I, Gloucester, am happy to oblige...!
202100.profile: I participated in a number of operations as a member of the Royal Navy. And while I was prepared to face my own sinking, I never would have imagined it would come thanks to a shortage of ammunition...
