Master, I swear to you that such a fatal mistake will absolutely never happen again.
202100.touch2: Take a seat over there. I am going to educate you on the proper way to treat a lady.
202100.mission: You have as yet uncompleted tasks... I will continue to remind you until all of your missions have been completed.
202100.home: Welcome home, Master. Have some tea. Now then, I must ask, you were fully committed to your duties during the sortie, yes?
202100.win_mvp: This is but a trifling victory. Master, should you be satisfied with such triviality... I would find that rather troubling.
202100.expedition: You should check on the commission team, Master. Do consider how it may affect their assessment of you.
couple_encourage: Have faith, the master will not let that happen again.
Madam Royal Knight, do take care of yourself.
202100.mail: Do check your mail... If you would prefer I not remind you, you need only check it sooner.
202100.feeling3: Master, you must keep a healthy, balanced diet. If you find it troublesome, I can cook your meals for you. Such is a maid's duty, after all.
202100.lose: I beg your pardon, Master. I have failed you.

301200.detail: The Leyte Gulf? I don't remember very much of it...
301200.login: Zzz... Fiiine, I'll get up in a second... The sun... is so warm... Zzz...
301200.feeling2: Movies? They aren't really my thing...
301200.mission_complete: Your rewards won't disappear even if you don't collect them... I think...
301200.main: If only I'd tried harder when I was in Truk...|I like this place, I don't need to hurt any of my allies here...|{namecode:25}... {namecode:22}... We're all together again in my dreams...
301200.feeling5: Zzz... Commander... It's fine to take some time off and nap every now... and then... Zzz...
301200.unlock: This place is... Huh? Are you the commander?! Ahem! Destroyer {namecode:24}, reporting in!
301200.feeling4: I tried too hard to be brave in Leyte Gulf... In the end I couldn't save anyone...
301200.feeling1: ... I can't sleep with you next to me...
301200.propose: This is... proof of a sisterly bond?! Commander, you want to be my sister? ... I've got it all wrong?! But that's what {namecode:130}-chan told me...
301200.profile: I'm {namecode:24}, a {namecode:19}-class destroyer. Luck? Kure and Sasebo ships have that, us Maizuru ships do not. I was unable to save {namecode:130} in Truk, but when I was in the Leyte Gulf I came running to {namecode:62}'s rescue. In the end I couldn't save everyone... but in my dreams we're all still together...
301200.mission: A-a mission? I hope it won't be difficult...
301200.home: Commander... *Yawn*... Today's weather is perfect for a nap...
301200.win_mvp: Hm? I'M the MVP?! What a lucky day!
301200.expedition: Someone's come back... Is it lunchtime now...?
couple_encourage: I'm nothing like you!
This time, I'll only fire on the enemy...
O... Onee-chan...
301200.mail: I don't really need a bedtime story...
301200.feeling3: {namecode:130}... I promise I'll help you this time...!
301200.lose: Where... am I? Who's shooting at me?

701022.detail: Królik is taking the day off. It'll be stronger the next time you see it. Trust me.
701022.touch: Eat as many blini as you want.
701022.login: Let's add a little sugar... Nom. Yummy. Comrade Commander, care to try a blini?
701022.mission_complete: Nice work, Comrade Commander. Now we're good on snacks for a long time ahead.
701022.main: *burp*... Warm drinks are nice.|I want to make Królik look cuter. Any good ideas how to do that, Comrade Commander?|Laffey, give me your rabbit ears for a second. Let's see how this looks... Hmm... It sort of fits, but not really...
701022.unlock: Hmm... If I tweak Królik around a bit like this... But, it'll probably be a problem if I don't finish this in one go... Guess I'll think about it while I eat. Mhm.
701022.drop_descrip: Hmm... If I tweak Królik around a bit like this... But, it'll probably be a problem if I don't finish this in one go... Guess I'll think about it while I eat. Mhm.
701022.touch2: Do you want to give Królik a swing?
701022.home: Comrade Commander, there's hot cocoa and coffee. Want some?

701021.detail: Hold on a second. Humph... Alright, I welcome you to my abode... The Manjuu looks nervous? Why's that?
701021.login: No need to drop off my rations today, comrade Commander. I'm not sleepy yet.
701021.main: *burp*... Drinking from a can doesn't feel the same...|Comrade Commander, this exercise is surprisingly fun since I don't need to do any thinking. You should try it too.|The ball and chain? It doesn't weigh much. See? Oh, sorry for startling you...
701021.unlock: Comrade Commander, are you here to see my room? Hm? That Шутки isn't funny? Then how about... did my room come to see you, comrade Commander?
701021.drop_descrip: Comrade Commander, are you here to see my room? Hm? That Шутки isn't funny? Then how about... did my room come to see you, comrade Commander?
701021.touch2: I don't have my кролик, so I'll have to use this ball and chain.
701021.expedition: It's warm here compared to my motherland's waters. I can drink while wearing little clothing and still be fine. *glug glug*

305111.detail: Mm... what a pleasant breeze. A fine day to embark on a new journey.
305111.login: Mhm, a fine morning. Have you had breakfast yet?
305111.main: When I don this uniform, I feel like I'm being called to my more youthful days... Ah, that's right! It's that excitement of going on a trip for the first time as a kid! Hehe~ |Back then, many of us went abroad to study with the Royal Navy. Hm, you can't picture me doing that? Want to see for yourself? Well, we're just a few minutes from the Royal dorms though. Hahaha!|Looking back, I sometimes miss those days... but right now, this fleet is where I belong.
305111.feeling5: I was thinking, what if I was still a schoolgirl, meeting you for the first time beneath the dancing cherry blossoms before becoming inseparable sweethearts... A scenario like that, might have been nice.
305111.unlock: I found quite the nostalgic outfit when I was cleaning my wardrobe. Let's see... "Prepare to come with me on a new journey!" How do I look, Commander?
305111.drop_descrip: I found quite the nostalgic outfit when I was cleaning my wardrobe. Let's see... "Prepare to come with me on a new journey!" How do I look, Commander?
305111.touch2: Hey! Knock that off! You're going to make me drop my luggage...
305111.home: Everyone has returned home safely. What a relief.

801022.detail: I joined the Kendo Club. I'm thinking it'll be good to hone my swordsmanship skills against my peers and build up my streng— Huh? What do you mean it's a different kind of sword!?
801022.touch: Aie! The wind! ...Erm!? Commander!? You, you didn't see anything, did you?
801022.main: Commander, have you seen Le Mars? If she's slacking off again, I don't know how she thinks she's going to pass the exam...|Study is much like swordsmanship, you have to take it seriously if you want to improve.|Commander, your collar's all twisted. Hold still, I'll get it— There, that's better!
801022.unlock: Even though I'm an Iris Libre squire, I'm currently working hard to have a rich student life. Um... maybe this is a bit too laid back?
801022.drop_descrip: Even though I'm an Iris Libre squire, I'm currently working hard to have a rich student life. Um... maybe this is a bit too laid back?
801022.touch2: S- such filthy, immoral behavior... You can't do this, Commander!
801022.mission: In study as in war, we must always remember the mission. Isn't that right, Commander?
801022.home: Commander, what do you say we have lunch together, if you have time?

801021.detail: Would you like some fresh fruit, Commander?
801021.touch: I know the other knights went out of their way to pick this dress for me... but I'm not used to all the frills and whatnot...
801021.battle: I hope... I don't get these clothes dirty...
801021.main: We don't usually get such fresh apples and tomatoes, so how about a mixed juice? It's good for your health! |No more fighting, no more wars... That's the peace that we're fighting to reclaim. |Commander, I heard that aromatherapy can help you recover from fatigue. Why don't you try growing some flowers?
801021.feeling5: If only this peace could last forever... Nay, as long as we work together, this won't merely be a dream. Right, Commander? Hehe~
801021.unlock: It's good to be able to stop and smell the roses every now and then. Um, Commander, would you be able to accompany me a bit longer?
801021.drop_descrip: It's good to be able to stop and smell the roses every now and then. Um, Commander, would you be able to accompany me a bit longer?
801021.touch2: Eep! N-next time, I won't hold back!

305110.detail: A flagship must lead from the vanguard. This is a self-evident truth.
305110.touch: Even the most hardworking people sometimes have lapses of judgment. It is my duty to admonish you in times like these.
305110.login: Until we've reclaimed our former glory, we must never stop pressing forward!
305110.battle: The fate of our country rests upon this battle!
305110.hp_warning: Keep calm! This battle is far from over!
305110.feeling2: Thinking about how I won't see old friends from back in my day ever again, it's... Well, never mind. I have people who look up to me now, and I can't let them down!
305110.mission_complete: Very well. I shall plunder... I mean, receive the spoils of victory!
305110.main: The victory at Tsushima did not occur by chance. |Royal cuisine? I'll pass... I've had enough of that. |Those things flying through the sky... Err, they're called "ear-playings," right?
305110.feeling5: You can't fire on all four boilers all the time. Listen, I'm going to look the other way while you take five... You've been wanting to nap on my lap? I-I guess that'd be okay...
305110.upgrade: Only the battlefield can separate the wheat from the chaff.
305110.unlock: I am the one who braved a hail of bullets and shells to return to my homeland with glory and victory. I am Mikasa, pre-dreadnought battleship of the Sakura Empire and flagship of the 1st Fleet, awaiting your command!
305110.feeling4: Yes, I can tell you've been working hard. B- but! That doesn't mean you get to start goldbricking now!
305110.propose: You still got a long way to go to earn my respect! ... Hehehe, so that's why I better stick by you♪ 'Til you're too good even for me.
305110.skill: Let every ship do her utmost!
305110.profile: I am Mikasa, a Shikishima-type battleship, and last of the Six-Six Fleet shipbuilding program. I served as the flagship of the Combined Fleet, and won a glorious victory that honored the name of our country across the world.
305110.touch2: You'd like me to be your dance partner at the next banquet? ... I-I suppose I have no choice...
305110.mission: Hmm, I'm in charge of today's fleet operations? Very well... the fate of our country rests... mmf! ... Why aren't you letting me speak?
305110.home: Excellent! The scales of war are tipping in our favor!
305110.win_mvp: Through righteousness comes prosperity. Such is the will of the heavens.
305110.expedition: Without robust logistics, even the mightiest fleets will turn into a disorderly mob.
couple_encourage: We fight together for humanity itself!
Steel yourself! And press the attack!
Never fear, the Sakura Empire is your ever steadfast ally.
Be careful. Misuse that power and we're worm food.
305110.mail: No matter how many medals and honors I receive... Ehehe~♪
305110.feeling3: If you don't have a plan to end a war, then you'd better not start one to begin with!
305110.lose: So this what it must have felt like to suffer through the Battle of Dan-no-ura...

303128.unlock: Commander... Ahh, from now on, shouldn't I call you "darling?" Come and hold my hand... Ah, at times like these, I just can't help but to want to eat you up, dar~ling~
303128.drop_descrip: Commander... Ahh, from now on, shouldn't I call you "darling?" Come and hold my hand... Ah, at times like these, I just can't help but to want to eat you up, dar~ling~
303128.touch2: Dar~ling, if you continue like this, I won't be able to hold back any more~ Hehe... just kidding~
303128.home: Surely you must be tired. Come take a nap in big sister's lap~
303128.win_mvp: As expected of my wonderful commander~

102261.detail: Craven was supposed to be cheer squad leader on account of she's older, but she ended up asking me to do it... I can't let her down. I gotta cheer hard!
102261.touch: Huh, you brought me water, Commander? Woaaahhh, no way...! Nng, my hero brought me water... I couldn't be happier...
102261.login: Commander, I got a great view of the games from here. Come watch with me~
102261.mission_complete: Commander, it's time to get your rewards, everyone's waiting for you to attend the ceremony~
102261.main: Ah, it's half time. That means we better get out there and cheer! Everybody ready? Let's get their blood pumping!|None of the other factions have serious cheerleaders like me or Craven. But I won't underestimate the ones they came up with either... I can't let them beat me~|Look at them out there on the field, shining like superheroes as they fight for victory... being a cheerleader sure is amazing!
102261.unlock: This really is a huge clash of all the biggest names from all the factions. It's one exciting match after another! I gotta cheer my hardest too. Eagle Union, go get 'em!
102261.drop_descrip: This really is a huge clash of all the biggest names from all the factions. It's one exciting match after another! I gotta cheer my hardest too. Eagle Union, go get 'em!
102261.home: Commander, you're just in time. The next match is about to start~

301144.detail: A letter to Santa? Hell yeah, I'll write one too! "One huge cut of steak, thanks"... Bam, perfect!
301144.login: Hop onto my sleigh and we'll go for a ride, Commander!
301144.main: Check it out, this outfit's real easy to move in! Useful in a fight, too... Huh? No fighting? Dammit...|Commander! Squeeze! ...See, Agano told me something nice would happen if I cradled your head like this! So, this "nice thing," what is it?|Well... Since I pulled the sleigh last time, now it's your turn to do it, Commander!
301144.feeling5: I saw you, Commander! You were stuffing the stockings with presents last night! Which can only mean... you're buddies with Santa Claus! Hehehe, I really love you, Commander!
301144.unlock: Christmas! The day Santa Claus drops by and leaves presents, right? Hell yeah, I'm pumped! Aren't you pumped too, Commander?
301144.drop_descrip: Christmas! The day Santa Claus drops by and leaves presents, right? Hell yeah, I'm pumped! Aren't you pumped too, Commander?
301144.home: Before we go to bed, we gotta hang our stockings by the fireplace! Man, I can't wait for tomorrow morning! Heheh!

101470.detail: This little guy is my friend, Mr. Bear. Umm... he's equipped with a lot of equipment. Take this right hand, for example... Wait, you can't aim at the Commander!
101470.touch: Mr. Bear, why don't you greet the Commander? Yes, normally, just like this... P-please keep your paws to yourself!
101470.feeling2: Commander, umm... to tell the truth, there's something I... i-it's nothing... forget I said anything...
101470.headtouch: Mr. Bear...? Oh, Commander... I don't think Mr. Bear meant to hit you, Commander...
101470.mission_complete: You completed the missions? That means that I'm free for the time being, right?
101470.main: I'd really like to get my hands on a few sets of the Iron Blood's rigging... Heh, hehehe...|Y-yes, you called? ...You didn't...? I'm sorry...|It's sunny out today... Though, it's not like sunny days are always good either.
101470.feeling5: Commander, am I helpful to you? I'm not a bother, am I? ...Mm, every time I hear your words of reassurance, I can relax a bit... Thank you very much, Commander.
101470.upgrade: I really don't think you need to go that far for someone like me...
101470.unlock: Phew... Finally got here in one piece... Ah, um, are you the commander? My name is Morrison. Yes, the Fletcher-class Morrison with way too many sisters...
101470.feeling4: Commander, um, could I have a bit of your time...? I wanted to get your input on what kinds of things I could do to improve upon Mr. Bear's specs...
101470.feeling1: Just like I thought, things are better without me around...
101470.propose: Phew... I've worked hard to prepare myself for this moment, so it's okay. Commander, if it's you, I'm okay with it...! Breathe in... Breathe out... C-C-Commander, u-u-um, I-I-I've finished preparing my heart! I-I'll be in your care!
101470.drop_descrip: Fletcher-class destroyer – Morrison, Hull Number DD-560.
101470.profile: I'm the Fletcher-class destroyer, Morrison. I participated in anti-submarine warfare and rescue missions with my allies... If there's anything you want me to do... I-I should be able to do it.
101470.touch2: M-Mr. Bear is on a rampage?!
101470.mission: Commander, if you need any help completing the missions, I don't mind...
101470.home: Commander, umm... I don't know if these will be of any use, but... (Morrison hands you some files)
101470.win_mvp: Whew... That should give me a bit of leeway...
101470.expedition: A commission has been completed. Umm, if you need any help, I don't mind...
couple_encourage: P-please allow me... to escort you!
101470.mail: Mr. Bear, bring the mail over to the Commander.
101470.feeling3: Commander, are you curious about Mr. Bear? T-Then, I'll introduce him to you.
101470.lose: Oww... Ugh, I want to go back to port...

302200.detail: Ah, if it isn't you, Commander. I was just making a snack. Could you taste it for pois... I mean, taste to see if it's done?
302200.touch: These documents are for me... Hm? That's unusual? I like to keep business and pleasure separate, you see.
302200.login: Commander, it's not yet time for work. Are you confident you didn't get the time wrong?
302200.battle: Let's give it everything we have.
302200.hp_warning: Dear me, it seems things have gotten rather serious.
302200.feeling2: I wonder what will happen today... *Giggle*, I'm looking forward to finding out.
302200.mission_complete: Commander, if you keep tasking your secretary with collecting the mission rewards, your brain will eventually turn to mush. Although, it might be interesting if that happened... *Giggle*♪
302200.main: Commander, if you're tired, why not play a game of leapfrog and jump around in the office? It'll help improve your blood circulation~|Though supporting from behind the lines is easy, doing so for long periods makes me grow tired of it...|Commander, are you in need of some rest? Hm? *Giggle*, I just felt like asking. Stay focused and continue your work~
302200.feeling5: Someone who toys with the person they like... Are you familiar with anyone like that, Commander? *Giggle*, perhaps it's me~
302200.upgrade: Please, have faith in the skill of this Agano-class light cruiser.
302200.unlock: Are you the Commander? My name is Agano. The pleasure is all mine, *giggle*... Never mind that, it was nothing. I'm eager to assume my position within your fleet.
302200.feeling4: Me? I'm fond of interesting things. Such as... the act of toying with you, Commander... *Giggle*, you'll have to excuse me for that~
302200.feeling1: Even breathing the same air as you do is unpleasant, Commander~
302200.propose: You have feelings for me, Commander? You wish to be with me forever? ... Why am I asking the questions here? *Giggle*, because, even for someone like me, wouldn't it be humiliating to have someone else take the initiative at moments like these...?
302200.drop_descrip: Agano-class light cruiser number one – Agano.
302200.skill: They don't call me "state of the art" for nothing~
302200.profile: I am Agano, the lead ship of the Agano-class. My abilities as a light cruiser are first-rate, though my birth was just a tad bit late... Commander, it is a pleasure to be in your service.
302200.mission: I went ahead and sorted out the new mission documents.
302200.home: Commander, fantastic work on the last sortie. May I offer you some hot tea?
302200.expedition: Commander, the girls that went on a commission have returned. If you keep twiddling your thumbs, you'll miss your chance to welcome them back...
couple_encourage: If you want to mess with Nagara, first you must get through me~
Noshiro, you'll have to develop a better relationship with the Commander.
302200.mail: Are you sure this isn't a love letter from that girl you know? *Giggle*♪
302200.feeling3: Commander, why don't we have a chat? Yes, I'm curious as to what kind of person you are.
302200.lose: How careless of me... I will undergo special training when we've returned. *Giggle*.

105100.detail: Celebration? Honor? Nothing else except for battles will draw my attention.
105100.touch: Commander, are we going into battle?
105100.login: I think I smell gunpowder, has the battle started already? Pfft... turns out it was only Vestal cooking.
105100.battle: Dear opponents, do NOT disappoint me!
105100.hp_warning: Now, this is a fun battle!
105100.feeling2: I don't know who granted us the title of BIG SEVEN. But if those two keep mentioning it non-stop, then the title should have some special meaning to it.
105100.mission_complete: Mission rewards... Darn, what a waste of time.
105100.main: Fighting beside my sisters is the happiest thing in the world! |I hate foul play, only fair duels are real battles! |Working? ...I don’t know much about that, I’ll just do whatever you tell me to do.
105100.feeling5: Look into my eyes, as my most trusted companions, is it even necessary to use words to express the feelings I have for you in my heart?
105100.upgrade: I really wanna try to shoot a volley from my main gun right now…
105100.unlock: I am Maryland, a member of the BIG SEVEN. “Fighting Mary”, yes, that's what they call me! I heard there are many battles ahead. I look forward to them all!
105100.feeling4: Not all problems can be solved by fighting? Well, I don't really believe that... but you always seem to find a way to solve things. After all, you are my favorite Commander.
105100.feeling1: A saying that I recently heard from my sister, “Never protest your loyalty to the weak”.
105100.propose: You really treasure these strange rings, do you? ...But since it's your decision, I'll go with it! From now on, I will protect you!
105100.drop_descrip: Colorado class battleship— Maryland, hull number BB-46
105100.skill: No matter how many times it takes, I will sink you again!
105100.profile: Eagle Union Colorado class battleship, ship no. 2 “Maryland”. As one of the BIG SEVEN, I often attended various celebrations. I escaped the attack on Pearl Harbor from behind Oklahoma. After undergoing retrofit, I successfully completed counter strike attacks on the Sakura Empire Navy. I participated in Operation Magic Carpet and received a total of seven battle stars. Commander, I just saw gunfire over there...oh, nevermind it was the sunset.
105100.touch2: Commander, our fighting power is not in that area of expertise.
105100.mission: If I don’t complete the mission, then I can’t get a battle star.
105100.home: Sigh, staying in port is so boring...
105100.win_mvp: Haha! This is just the appetizer before the main course!
105100.expedition: Even though commissions are an important part of the war, but I'm just not interested in them.
couple_encourage: I will protect you this time!
105100.mail: When writing a reply back, should I carry an anti-aircraft gun with me...
105100.feeling3: The war cannot be won by a single person. Without true sisters fighting alongside you and a reliable backline supporting you, no matter how strong you are, your defeat is inevitable!

303122.detail: Commander, would you like to pet the puppy? She seems to have taken a liking to you~
303122.touch: Just the two of us, enjoying the solace of winter together... doesn't it set just the right mood?
303122.login: Commander, are you cold? Come and receive some warmth from your big sister~
303122.main: nil|Commander, would you like to take a stroll with your big sister? I'd like some peace and quiet with just the two of us~ |Akashi-chan? Don't fall asleep on top of the commander~
303122.unlock: Oh my, it's begun to snow. Commander, should we find a nice, quiet place to enjoy the view?
303122.drop_descrip: Oh my, it's begun to snow. Commander, should we find a nice, quiet place to enjoy the view?

105170.detail: Thanks for finishing the equipment inspection. All systems nominal! ...Oh my, you seem to be unable to take your eyes off me~ Not that it bothers me though? Besides, don'tcha like this sort of stuff?
105170.touch: I'll take any work-related requests, but anything outside of that... won't come cheap. Just kidding~♪
105170.login: Glad you made it. Do you already have a plan for what you wanna do? And how do I factor into those plans?
105170.battle: Everyone, Level 1 combat readiness! Set sail!
105170.hp_warning: I know just the thing to turn this situation around!
105170.feeling2: We'll only get in each other's way if we keep an ambivalent relationship. Say, don'tcha think getting touchy-feely might help break the ice? ...Just kidding~ See, you're already not as nervous~ Hehehe~♪
105170.headtouch: Done having your fun yet? Hehe, now it's my turn~♪ Take a seat!
105170.mission_complete: Since we already got the hard stuff out of the way, why not take a little break? It's gonna be pretty easy to prioritize whatever is left~
105170.main: Iowa versus Yamato, huh? A real classic. Don'tcha just love that kind of stuff?|I go for the fruity stuff~ green apple, orange, and soda water. As for coffee... Not my favorite, I guess?|How much stuff should I be doing as your secretary? ...Lemme think, how does 40% sound? If I did everything, wouldn't that make me the commander? Heh.|About that matter... I must admit that you have a point, Commander. How about taking my suggestion next time though?|It's now the age of carriers? ...Dunno about that. If carriers are able to evolve, what's to say that battleships can't also evolve?|They call me Big J or the Black Dragon of the Eagle Union! ...What, got a problem with talking myself up a bit?
105170.feeling5: Commander, would you prefer I take the lead, or would you rather do it? Hold up~ I'll see for myself when the time is right, so there's no need for you to answer in words. After all, don'tcha just love being toyed with~?
105170.upgrade: Some say that the age of battleships is over. They haven't met the Iowa class.
105170.unlock: The indomitable Black Dragon of the Eagle Union is none other than me, New Jersey! You're about to witness true power! Haha, just messing~♪ Don'tcha just love flashy introductions?
105170.feeling4: My my, look who's all run down today... I knew it, you've been overworking yourself. C'mere, lie down here and let me take care of you. Yeah, my thighs make for a pretty good pillow substitute huh? Don'tcha just love this kind of stuff~?
105170.feeling1: Ah, so you're the kind of person who makes girls cry. Yeah, you'd better feel bad about it.
105170.propose: Commander, I can already hear everything you're thinking. As long as you're fine with it, I don't have any objections~ After all, I still owe you a proper confession, don't I? Hehe, don'tcha think that's what mutual love is supposed to look like?
105170.drop_descrip: Iowa-class battleship – New Jersey, Hull Number BB-62.
105170.skill: Fire control, I'm counting on you!
105170.profile: I am battleship New Jersey, the indomitable Black Dragon of the Eagle Union. When I say "indomitable," I'm not just tooting my own horn, hehe~♪ If you knew more about me, you'd know exactly what I'm talking about.
105170.touch2: Commander, don'tcha just love being put on the defensive? In more ways than one~♪
105170.mission: Did you already accept this mission? Sounds good, let's take care of it together.
105170.home: Wanna check the battle results~♪ Yeah? Who do you wanna start with? Oh, you'll do it yourself? I'll listen in while enjoying some ice cream over here.
105170.win_mvp: Course: steady! Objective: completed! Enemies who can stop us: none! Heheh, don'tcha love it when things go smoothly?
105170.expedition: Your commission fleet's back. Are your words of praise not the best reward you can give them? Hehe~♪
couple_encourage: A larger-caliber Iowa? No, not quite...
As if I'd lose to some carriers!
Freedom and firepower: an unstoppable force!
Oh? Finally, a worthy opponent? How interesting~
We owe a lot to you, Miss Heroine.
105170.mail: You've got new mail. Heh, dont'cha just love the anticipation~?
105170.feeling3: Look at that, you're already starting to chat me up. So, what's on your mind today? Something a bit more technical? Small talk about daily life? ...Oh, you want me to choose?
105170.lose: Unbelievable... I'm actually getting cornered?! ...I'm not gonna be able to sleep 'til I figure out how to set things straight!

319010.detail: My weapon? ...Hyah! Eh? I look really cool? D-don't say that, I barely know how to use it...
319010.touch: Am I carrying main guns again? ...Ah, sorry, I spaced out a bit...
319010.login: Welcome back, Commander. Is there anything I can transport... Err, I mean, is there anything I can help you with...?
319010.hp_warning: It's just a scratch... Don't worry, I can keep going!
319010.feeling2: My rigging is a bit different from that of the other girls. Want to learn more...? Mm, why don't you come take a seat on my deck then?
319010.headtouch: Oh...! S-sorry, did I hit you with my tail...?
319010.mission_complete: Mission complete~ That's one fewer thing to worry about.
319010.main: 1, 2, 3... Commander, the supplies you've given me to transport are all accounted for. Hm? It's all right, you don't have to get everyone to help me carry it. It's not very heavy...|♪~ Commander, I brought you your tea. Adding a bit of milk will give it a Royal Navy flair... how about it?|Commander, how about decorating your window with a windchime? Enjoying a refreshing breeze while enjoying this delicate sound will surely make you feel better~
319010.feeling5: Phew... Ah, Commander, are you feeling better now? I've brought iced milk, sweets, and everyone's well-wishes. Ehehe~ If you'd like me to wash your back again, just let me know.
319010.upgrade: Hmm... Was I supposed to feel different...?
319010.unlock: Well met, Commander. I am Kashino, munition ship of the Sakura Empire. Hmm... I may be a rather peculiar ship, but... if there's anything I can help with, please entrust it to me... is that acceptable?
319010.feeling4: Commander, if you're tired, why not take a bath? Afterwards, if you enjoy some fresh milk, you'll be sure to feel— C-Commander?? What's wrong? Should I take you to the infirmary...?
319010.feeling1: I can bring you all the supplies in the world, but you don't seem to be capable of using them well...
319010.propose: As a munition ship, I may not be very useful in combat. However, as long as you believe in me and cherish me... I'll try to be as useful as I can in other ways...! Mhm!
319010.profile: My name is Kashino. My favorite hobby is relaxing in the hot springs, and my weight and height are... Ack, that's not what I'm supposed to be saying! Excuse me... Um, I was the ship that was created to transport the Yamato-class's 40cm Type 94 gun, but I also participated in various transport missions before finally being sunk by a submarine... Hmm, is that good enough...?
319010.mission: Do you still have missions to complete? Please be mindful of the deadlines.
319010.home: Phew... Oh, Commander, welcome back. I just finished stashing the supplies that the others brought back into the warehouse. The inventory? Um... please give me a moment.
319010.win_mvp: This sense of elation is rather mysterious... Mm...
319010.expedition: The commission team has returned safely. Let's go greet them. Having that said, I'm used to being in their position though, not the other way around~
couple_encourage: I've brought your armaments!
319010.mail: There's a letter on this pile of supplies...? Oh, it's addressed to you, Commander. Here you go.
319010.feeling3: I often play with the little destroyers. Like this... I put one on each shoulder and pretend like I'm some giant monster or robot... Yes, it's quite fun~♪
319010.lose: Ugh... It's hard for me to keep up with the actual warships...

102060.detail: Ah, Commander's looking... I have to behave like a big sister!
102060.touch: Mgh, don't touch me like that... My big sister image would be ruined!
102060.login: Commander, if you ever run into a problem, please tell me!
102060.battle: I'll show you what the tons-of-guns doctrine is really worth!
102060.feeling2: Being a big sister isn't just about looking like one, you need to have the personality of one as well. That's why you can depend on me all you want~!
102060.mission_complete: Our mission rewards have arrived. I'll give my share of the rewards to my little sisters.
102060.main: Not being a flagship sure is more peaceful...|San Francisco was terrible to me! Just once is tolerable for accidental friendly fire, but she shot me well over ten times!|Shooting down aircraft is my specialty. Want me to teach you how to do it, Commander?
102060.feeling5: ... Huh? You want me to take the initiative? O-o-o-o-of course, I don't mind! I-I mean, I'm your big sister after all, so it's my job to guide you!
102060.upgrade: Let me handle things from now on!
102060.unlock: I'm the anti-aircraft cruiser Atlanta. Kept you waiting, huh, Commander? But from now on you can rest easy and let me handle everything!
102060.feeling4: Are you fond of assertive big sister type characters? That is to say... someone like me...
102060.feeling1: Sometimes I'm happy that I'm not actually your big sister...
102060.propose: Thank you... From now on I'll... What? You'd prefer it if I took the initiative and gave it to you instead? Y-you have a point... Okay then, should we do it again from the start?
102060.drop_descrip: Atlanta-class light cruiser – Atlanta, Hull Number CL-51!
102060.profile: I'm the anti-aircraft cruiser Atlanta... I was the flagship of the 10th and 11th Atlantic cruising fleet and I've taken part in nearly every military operation in the Pacific. Even the President has given me praise!
102060.mission: So, does this mean you're leaving all your unfinished missions to me, Commander?
102060.home: That's the Commander I know. No problem for you at all, right?
102060.win_mvp: All targets eliminated. Requesting new mission!
102060.expedition: Commander, the commission's done. Are we gonna go welcome the girls back?
102060.mail: You've got new mail! I wonder if any of the messages are from my sisters...
102060.feeling3: The bigger the better, don't you think? ...Hey! What are you staring at?! Gee, sorry for not being big enough, I guess!
102060.lose: Argh, this is bad... My big sister image is ruined...

401200.detail: I'll make all your concerns go "poof!" How's that, Commander? Feel better?
401200.touch: Hmm? You want to go on a run with me?
401200.battle: I'm the flagship? Fine by me! Everyone, follow me!
401200.feeling2: As long as you keep running, you'll leave behind all your hardship and anxiety. Commander, come find me any time you're feeling down.
401200.mission_complete: Marathon, marathon! I'll definitely take first place this time.
401200.main: Commander, let me teach you the right way to breathe while running. It's good for both attacking and retreating!|As long as I'm in a good mood, I can enjoy any scenery!|Protschny? Don't call me by that name!
401200.feeling5: You idiot... All right, stop blushing and stammering. I like you. So, do you feel the same way about me?
401200.unlock: Z20, Karl Galster, reporting in! Where's my welcoming party?
401200.feeling4: If you never tell others how you feel about them, they'll never understand. You get that, right?
401200.feeling1: The moment I saw you, all the fatigue from running kicked in at once. I'm out, time to rest!
401200.propose: Say, I heard there's a tradition in the East where couples will drink with their arms intertwined. Haha, come on, Commander! Don't be shy!
401200.skill: Gotta smile during battle as well!
401200.profile: I am Z20 Karl Galster, Iron Blood Z-class 1936-Type destroyer, the sole survivor of the Z17 type destroyers. After being being handed over to the Northern Union, I was renamed "прочный." Being separated from my sisters and living alone sure was rough...
401200.touch2: Hehe, how do you like my curves?
401200.mission: Let's prepare for the celebrations before we start~
401200.home: Good job! Let's go find some place to relax.
401200.expedition: Ah, our friends have returned! Let's go welcome them back!
401200.mail: A letter for you, eh? I don't think I should be the one to open your mail.
401200.feeling3: What's wrong? Something bugging you? I promise you'll feel better if we go run a marathon together!
401200.lose: Oof... even I mess up sometimes... just sometimes~

10700031.detail: In order to create even bigger bubbles... slowly... like this... Eek! Say something if you're there!
10700031.touch: Popping the bubbles? I didn't know you had a childish side to you.
10700031.login: Oh, it's you. You've come at the perfect time. Get behind me and give me a push!
10700031.headtouch: Eek! ...Hey, can you not touch me out of the blue?!
10700031.main: Spending time here with you all is actually pretty nice. What are we doing next?|Since we're here on vacation, we've just got to try some of the local cuisine. You've done your research, right?|Hey, just because it's vacation doesn't mean you can slack off! Don't you even dream of napping. Come and accompany me to the beach!
10700031.unlock: Blowing bubbles while sitting on a swing... It might seem a bit childish, but there's nothing wrong with enjoying activities like these every so often.
10700031.drop_descrip: Blowing bubbles while sitting on a swing... It might seem a bit childish, but there's nothing wrong with enjoying activities like these every so often.
10700031.touch2: Hey, stop that! You creep! Degenerate! Absolute pervert!
10700031.home: Since you're back, come keep me company. It's not every day I get to take a vacation. It'd be such a waste not to enjoy it to the fullest!

319011.detail: If there's anything lacking about these hot springs, it's the fact that this place is too small... If you're not careful, it's easy to slip or to bump into various things...
319011.login: Commander, are you enjoying the water? Yes, I love the hot springs here~
319011.main: Phew... That feels so good... My shoulders aren't stiff anymore~ Commander, thank you for telling me about this place~ |M-my swimsuit, um... Commander's going to see... Erm, please disregard that!|A nice bottle of milk after a refreshing soak really hits the spot~ Let's get another bottle later~♪ ...Um, I knocked the first one over when I slipped earlier...
319011.unlock: Ack... Owww... My apologies, Commander, I seem to have slipped on something... At times, it's hard to notice things I'm about to step on... Ugh...
319011.drop_descrip: Ack... Owww... My apologies, Commander, I seem to have slipped on something... At times, it's hard to notice things I'm about to step on... Ugh...
319011.touch: Shall I... wash your back for you?
319011.home: I've kept the fresh milk in the fridge back there. After you've finished bathing, please feel free to help yourself~
319011.mail: By the way, Commander, there was a letter for you... Sorry, I forgot to report it earlier...
319011.lose: Oww... My luck isn't so good today...

10700021.detail: How does this yukata look? ...It looks pretty on me? I'd be happy if that were the case...
10700021.touch: This stone is so slippery, it's hard to stand on... Eek! T-thank you, Commander... That was a close one.
10700021.login: Good afternoon, Commander. Huh...? How long have I been waiting? There's nothing to worry about, I just got here myself.
10700021.main: There's a flower pattern on the inside of this umbrella. I love to look up whenever I use it because it looks as if flowers are blooming above my head, and that's so pretty.|The fireworks exploding above our heads and the fireworks reflected on the surface of the water... they're both very pretty.|Watching fireworks next to the other people really feels exciting and festive, but I also like the relaxed atmosphere of watching fireworks from afar like this.
10700021.unlock: Oh, the fireworks display is starting. I'm planning to meet up with the others after this, but... Why don't we spend some time enjoying the view here first?
10700021.drop_descrip: Oh, the fireworks display is starting. I'm planning to meet up with the others after this, but... Why don't we spend some time enjoying the view here first?
10700021.touch2: Eeek! ...Don't do something like that all of a sudden! I almost tripped!
10700021.home: In the summer, it's so hot, even in the evening... I'm going to go buy something cool to drink.

102130.detail: Unlike those Sakura Empire ships, I don't bring any misfortune to my allies. Probably… I hope…
102130.touch: You get good luck if you touch me? I've never heard of that before.
102130.login: Luck never stays with one person for too long, Commander. We should make the best use of it while we still have it.
102130.battle: Did you hear that? That was the sound of the Winds of Fortune!
102130.hp_warning: Hehe... my luck is second to none!
102130.feeling2: Things might have gone differently at Kolombangara, had Helena been there...
102130.mission_complete: Hehe... You're so spoiled, Commander... Okay, before you go and collect those rewards, you can stay here for a while and rest if you want.
102130.main: What are you looking at, Commander?|Helena, your SG radar can't detect underwater threats.|Arizona, even if you'll never forget what happened that day, you shouldn't let it wear you down so much.
102130.feeling5: Whew… Cleaning is always such a pain… Hey, why don't we go on a date somewhere, Commander?
102130.upgrade: Luck comes and goes. You can't depend on in it forever.
102130.unlock: Hello, I'm St. Louis, but I'm called Lucky Lou. Hey, Commander, don't you think it's your lucky day, finding me like this?
102130.feeling4: Hehe~ I know about all the secret things you have hidden in your room, Commander~!
102130.propose: Oh dear, why are you giving me a present all of a sudden... Ah, I see, it's one of these... Okay, could I ask you to put it on my finger for me, Commander?
102130.drop_descrip: Brooklyn-class Light Cruiser – St. Louis, Hull Number CL-49!
102130.profile: I'm St. Louis, Helena's big sister. I got my nickname, Lucky Lou, from getting through the attack on Pearl Harbor unscathed. After that, however, my missions didn't go all that well. I guess luck really does come and go after all...
102130.touch2: This isn't something you should do outside, Co-man-der~
102130.mission: Hey, Commander, you should prepare yourself for a real surprise.
102130.home: Always remember: "the feud chair is unpredictable"… Hmm, I heard that from someone, but who…?
102130.win_mvp: Hehe~ That wasn't all thanks to luck.
102130.expedition: Hmm... Okay, I'll go greet the returning commission team with these clothes.
couple_encourage: Helena, don't focus purely on victory or defeat this time!
I suppose you could call us the Lucky Unit!
102130.mail: New mail? It must be good news!
102130.feeling3: Want me to help you clean your office, Commander? ... You don't!?
102130.lose: Today is not my lucky day…

10700011.detail: I've tried to replicate the takoyaki and yakisoba they sell here, but I just can't get the flavor right for some reason. Isn't that weird?
10700011.touch: Hehehe~ Don't you love festivals? Anyway, where should we go next?
10700011.login: Oh, hi! I'm glad you came to the festival too, Commander! Do you want to take a look around?
10700011.main: What's wrong? Why are you hanging over there, Commander? Are you tired from wading through the crowds?|It's kind of annoying to walk around in a yukata. I've got to pay extra attention so I don't trip ov– Oh, shoot!|You came at just the perfect time, Commander! I just bought ramune and they gave me an extra bottle. Here, let's enjoy them!
10700011.unlock: Good evening, Commander! Are you also taking a break? If so, let's go get some candied apples and have a little chat~♪
10700011.drop_descrip: Good evening, Commander! Are you also taking a break? If so, let's go get some candied apples and have a little chat~♪
10700011.touch2: C-Commander! Please stop, or you'll open my yukata's bottom!
10700011.home: Wow, you've really been out and about! Should we take a break and sit on that bench over there?

303124.detail: I'm pretty sure it was on purpose, but these clothes are very revealing... Hehehe. Big sister thinks it's cute when you're honest like this.
303124.touch: Commander, keep at it~ Big sister is always by your side♡
303124.login: Commander~ Please do your best today♡ *smooch*
303124.battle: Commander~ Work hard on leading the fleet, okay♡
303124.main: Commander, are you tired? Hehehe, why don't you lay down and rest for a bit? Where, you ask? Well of course... right here~♡|Sigh, it's a pain to have to keep maintaining this pose... Commander, won't you help big sister up?|Akashi, you said you wanted to publish a lingerie photobook starring me, right? Then... Commander, would you like to see those photos?
303124.feeling5: Commander, next time we take photos, I'm counting on you. That's right. We can spend some quality time together, just the two of us... For some reason, I get the feeling that we're going to end up with an album that's for your eyes only, hehe♡
303124.unlock: So, you want big sister to be your "fleet queen"? You got it. But you'd better give it your all out there, or else I'll be upset with you!
303124.drop_descrip: So, you want big sister to be your "fleet queen"? You got it. But you'd better give it your all out there, or else I'll be upset with you!
303124.win_mvp: Me being the fleet's showgirl, isn't this much to be expected~?

305118.detail: Well, perfect timing. Hm... It looks like this size should fit you... As the one in charge, you can't neglect stocking up on necessities. Once we're in the middle of battle, even your best clothes can get all torn up in the blink of an eye. Make sure you to get some spares while we're still in the lull of peace.
305118.touch: Urgh, how in the world do you use this cellular phone thing? ...Grrrr...
305118.login: I can't get used to calling you "Dear" or you calling me "Honey"... Calling each other by what we already do would be easier? Very well, as long as you're fine with it...
305118.battle: Vanquish all evil! Crush the enemy!
305118.mission_complete: Very good. Well done! We're done with the mission! You really should teach Zuikaku and the others how you do it.
305118.main: My Commander, don't slack on your studies. If you'd like, I'd be happy to teach you personally.|Tonight's menu... How about I make you naval curry that originates from a port I have an affinity with? Of course, it's simply exquisite.|So those are "airplanes." The true potential of new things are often overlooked for quite some time. Do your best to not do the same.
305118.unlock: I, battleship Mikasa, from now until eternity, pledge to you my undying love and devotion. May we help each other, encourage each other, and walk side-by-side on the same path. I hope to meet your expectations, as unworthy as I may be.
305118.drop_descrip: I, battleship Mikasa, from now until eternity, pledge to you my undying love and devotion. May we help each other, encourage each other, and walk side-by-side on the same path. I hope to meet your expectations, as unworthy as I may be.
305118.touch2: You're working very hard, so I guess I'll allow this much...
305118.mission: Oi! Don't doze off on me! I promise I'll let you rest after you read through the mission!
305118.home: You brought everyone back safely, without a hitch! Spectacularly done, I must say. Hahaha!
305118.win_mvp: As long as you put your mind to it, there's no war you can't win! Redouble your efforts, and keep up the good work!
305118.mail: Hehe♪ These medals and awards... are things I obtained with you by my side. Go ahead, burn the sight into your mind~
305118.lose: Are you telling me it's impossible, even with the Commander at my back...?

301140.touch: Grr... Stop treating me like a kid.
301140.login: Ugh, Commander... "Shake paws"?! Are you making fun of me?!
301140.battle: Awoo! I'm not gonna go easy on you all!
301140.hp_warning: I'll show you what the Nightmare of Solomon looks like!
301140.mission_complete: Commander, Commander, hurry up and check the rewards to see if there are any snacks!
301140.main: Commander, seriously, stop throwing that frisbee at me. I'm not a dog~!|*Sniff sniff* I smell meat! Where is it?! Tell me right now!|It's so boring when I don't get to fight... Commander, wanna have a go? Let's do it!
301140.feeling5: Commander, rub my belly… Huh? I've heard you should show your belly button when you're apologizing to someone... Next time I mess up I'll let you rub my belly, so don't get angry at me... Th-that tickles, ahahaha!
301140.upgrade: Commander, take me out to the sea already. I really wanna test out my guns~
301140.unlock: I'm {namecode:16}, fourth ship of the {namecode:15}-class. I'll tell you this right now: I'm pretty loud at night, so brace yourself.
301140.feeling4: My sisters are still laughing at me and it's your fault! What are you gonna do to fix it? I won't let you off the hook with... *Giggle*... with just a... *Giggle*... headpat...
301140.propose: Pro... mise? What's that? You mean from now you'll always pat my head, never get angry when I screw up, and let me eat tons of tasty food?! Hell yeah, I'm in!
301140.skill: Turn to junk floating in the Solomon Sea!
301140.profile: I'm {namecode:16}! People call me the "Mad Dog of Solomon"! Heheh, I sound pretty strong, don't I? I'd never lose in a brawl! Hm? It's snack time? Commander, tell me where those snacks are!
301140.touch2: Grr… I'll stuff you into guns and send you off to space, you damn molester!
301140.mission: Another new mission? You adults sure are a pain...
301140.home: Commander, Commander, wanna eat something together?
301140.win_mvp: Missions involving breaking stuff are my specialty!
301140.expedition: Commander, a commission's been... A compliment's good enough, so stop patting my head!
couple_encourage: Monkey Corps {namecode:15}, strike!
I'm neither a dog nor a monkey!
301140.mail: Hey, mail for you. Is it a challenge for me? I won't lose!
301140.feeling3: "Grr! Who will I bite today?" How's that? Awfully violent, right? ... Good, now my sisters will stop telling me I'm like a dog outside of battle!
301140.lose: Damn it, I can't believe… I lost…

102262.detail: It was really hard to find a swimsuit that would fit my bust... Luckily, I was able to find this swimsuit at the last minute! It fits my chest perfectly, but... my poor hips are chafing... Ow...
102262.touch: If it isn't coconut milk! Is it okay to accept such a precious gift? ...Hehe. I'm absolutely elated to receive a precious present from my hero!
102262.login: *Click!* Welcome back, Commander! Heehee~ I couldn't stop myself from taking a picture of my beloved hero enjoying the beach!
102262.main: Looks like everyone's pumped up for the beach volleyball tournament! If only my... weren't so big. They make it hard to move around...|Oh yeah. How dashing does My Hero look when swimming? Do you zoom by others while going at 100 miles per hour? Hehehe~| If you compete in the tournament, I'll cheer you on with all I've got! Go! Go! Come on! You can do it! M-Y-H-E-R-O!
102262.unlock: "Superhero spin-off! The superhero who saved the world is enjoying a hard-earned vacation on the afternoon beach with the sidekick!" ... Hehe, Commander, a tagline like that sounds pretty cool, doesn't it?
102262.drop_descrip: "Superhero spin-off! The superhero who saved the world is enjoying a hard-earned vacation on the afternoon beach with the sidekick!" ... Hehe, Commander, a tagline like that sounds pretty cool, doesn't it?
102262.touch2: Woah?! I-If you touch it like that, it's going to snap!!
102262.home: Commander, are you in Sleep Mode? Then please, rest well! ...You don't have to worry about me. I've already rested for a bit, and I was thinking about heading out to make my rounds anyway!

10700061.detail: Did you see my mad drumming skills~? I'll work hard to make sure everyone else feels as hyped for the festival as I am~☆
10700061.touch: Commander, do you want to try drumming on the taiko? Nihihi, I wonder if you really can drum better than I can~
10700061.login: Oh, Commander! Have you come to gaze upon my gallant figure?
10700061.main: I can see the festival grounds clearly from here! Now now, I wonder where the Commander might be~?|Aren't these clothes like, super fashionable~?|Commander, let's compete in some festival games! Cork gun shooting, yo-yo fishing, goldfish scooping... Nihihi~ Just letting you know, I'm not going to lose~!
10700061.unlock: Summer's all about the festivals, and Ami Futami's the queen of festivals! Even the fireworks soaring through the sky can't hold a candle to how brilliant Ami is, so keep your eyes on me, Commander~♪
10700061.drop_descrip: Summer's all about the festivals, and Ami Futami's the queen of festivals! Even the fireworks soaring through the sky can't hold a candle to how brilliant Ami is, so keep your eyes on me, Commander~♪
10700061.touch2: Whoa there! My sash is going to come undone~!
10700061.home: It's break time~ I sure would like to go around the carts and eat a bunch of tasty stuff~ *Glance*

10700051.detail: It's important to stay hydrated and replenish your electrolytes when exercising in the heat. Otherwise you could get a heatstroke!
10700051.touch: Check out this serve! ...Heheh! Another point to me! It's still not too late to give up, Commander!
10700051.login: Good morning. Just give me a moment while I roll up my futon... Wait, I said wait! You can't come in yet!
10700051.main: Exercising? Indoors? In the middle of summer? I mean... It's better than doing it under the sweltering sun, but not by a lot...|The ventilation in here actually isn't half-bad. You just part the sliding doors and it gets almost as cool as an air-conditioned room... Okay, maybe that's an exaggeration...|Are you all right? You look like you're about to pass out. Knowing you, you're probably pushing yourself too hard. Here, take this sports drink.
10700051.unlock: Sorry, what? A paddle showdown? Commander, please... You play that in a kimono, not a yutaka. But if you insist... If I win, you're buying me an ice cream!
10700051.drop_descrip: Sorry, what? A paddle showdown? Commander, please... You play that in a kimono, not a yutaka. But if you insist... If I win, you're buying me an ice cream!
10700051.touch2: Eek! H-hey! It's not okay to do that stuff in the heat of the game!
10700051.home: How about we take a quick break? And no, before you ask: I'm NOT conceding the match. We'll pick up where we left off after I've had some water!

10700041.detail: Oh! Thank you for coming all this way in the blistering heat. Let's see... I should have something cool to snack on in the fridge.
10700041.touch: This yukata feels so much breezier than the clothes I usually wear. I recommend trying one for yourself, Commander.
10700041.login: Whew, it's so hot today. Make sure you drink plenty of water so you don't get dehydrated.
10700041.main: As much as I love cooling off in an air-conditioned room, it's also nice to sit on the veranda and just feel the breeze.|Oh dear, the winds have died down. Then I'll instead use this paper fan to help you keep cool, Commander.|There are many kinds of wind chimes in the world. Some are made of metal, others are made of glass. I enjoy listening for the slight differences in sound between them all.
10700041.unlock: Listening to the wind flow through the chimes on the porch seems to carry the summer heat right away. Commander, would you also like to come unwind with me?
10700041.drop_descrip: Listening to the wind flow through the chimes on the porch seems to carry the summer heat right away. Commander, would you also like to come unwind with me?
10700041.touch2: Are you okay, Commander? You look like you're suffering from a heatstroke... Wait here. I'll fetch you some ice and a sports drink right away.
10700041.home: Welcome back from the summer heat, Commander. I'll get you a bottle of cold tea.

101471.detail: Benson told me all about the ins and outs of Planet Bunny... Huh? Is something amiss?
101471.touch: C-can I take a nap yet...?
101471.login: It's a bit embarrassing, but... it's surprisingly comfortable...
101471.headtouch: M-my ears are going to fall off...
101471.main: I wonder if I should take Stanly's advice and turn Mr. Bear into "Rabbit Mode"...|I'm so jealous of all the people that get to wear cute clothes... Y-you think I'm cute, too...?|I-it's spicy? Was it Thatcher? No, it could have been Kalk...
101471.unlock: Zzz... Commander? S-sorry, I fell asleep for a bit... Uh, umm, what would you like me to do...?
101471.drop_descrip: Zzz... Commander? S-sorry, I fell asleep for a bit... Uh, umm, what would you like me to do...?
101471.touch2: Commander, um, please show some self-restraint...
101471.home: Commander, would you like some tea...?
101471.mail: Mr. Bear, take the mail to the Commander... Oh, Mr. Bear isn't here right now...

301141.detail: It's cold? It doesn't feel cold at all to me!
301141.touch: Shiratsuyu, Shigure, let's have a snowball fight!
301141.login: The hell you looking so sad for, Commander? C'mon, let's roll around in the snow together!
301141.battle: Snowball fights are my specialty as well!
301141.main: It's too warm in here, it's making me sleepy... Mmmh... Commander... meat... so yummy...|Woof! Focus fire on the commander! Victory shall be mine!|Gotta eat hotpot during winter, right? Hotpot? Let's make some hotpot!
301141.unlock: Come out of your office, Commander! You'll become lazy if you huddle up next to the heater all day! Let's go out and play in the snow!
301141.drop_descrip: Come out of your office, Commander! You'll become lazy if you huddle up next to the heater all day! Let's go out and play in the snow!

107019.detail: Commander, if you run into a mental problem, you have to solve it on your own. Staring at me won't help you.
107019.touch: I will answer any question you have for me. However, is that really alright for you, Commander?
107019.main: If we make a little progress each day, we'll be sure to achieve great results one day|This fleet feels different from when I first came. With your hard work, Commander, we can do anything.|We have to punish naughty children. Don't you agree, Commander?
107019.unlock: Listen to what I say, or I'll have to step on you!
107019.drop_descrip: Listen carefully or I'll step on you!

202230.detail: Um, sorry I made such a mess... Sheffield tried to teach me how to clean, but I'm a lot worse at it than I expected... Ahaha...
202230.touch: As your secretary ship, I am responsibile for everything in all of the reports.
202230.login: Good morning. Here is your work for the day... *Sigh*...
202230.battle: All ships, forward...! Form up on me!
202230.hp_warning: I have to get the others to safety, at least...!
202230.feeling2: Commander, do you have something for me? I can handle anything... Oh, but only if you're okay with me...
202230.mission_complete: Commander, I've finished tallying up the mission rewards. Do look them over.
202230.main: Commander, let's work as hard as we ever do, eh?|Commander, do you think a Lady of the Royal Navy should be more elegant? Not like the maids, I mean Fiji and Jamaica... They stand out quite a bit... is that alright?|I envy the Knight Commander. If only I could comport myself so... Sorry about that. Forget I said anything.
202230.feeling5: I think I'd probably be better off being all cool like Sheffield than trying to smile all the time like Fiji... Right? If I every so often let slip a smile that could catch the Commander's eye... Oh, um, forget everything I said just now!
202230.upgrade: Swiftsure, swiftly and surely, everyone is counting on you...!
202230.unlock: I am Swiftsure, a light cruiser of the Royal Navy... If it is not too much for one such as myself to ask, I would like to support your fleet in whatever way I can.
202230.feeling4: The Commander told me to help Jamaica fix up her bike. Hehehe, it turned out to be a lot more fun than I thought... Oh, Commander, sorry... about that... just now...
202230.feeling1: Someone like me deserves a Commander like this...
202230.propose: I'm really sorry about all this. Are you honestly okay with someone like me...? The way I am...? Umm, if you're alright with me, then I'll gladly be your partner! Commander, thank you so much!
202230.drop_descrip: I am Swiftsure, a light cruiser of the Royal Navy... If it is not too much for one such as myself to ask, I would like to support your fleet in whatever way I can.
202230.skill: Get the timing right... I should be able to do this!
202230.profile: I am Swiftsure, of the Royal Navy. I joined towards the end of the war, but with it winding down and fate taking some odd twists and turns, I wasn't able to perform as expected. If it pleases you, I will serve the fleet with everything I have. Oh, but if it doesn't, you need not worry about me...
202230.touch2: Commander, um... I think fleet regulations call this kind of thing "inappropriate..."
202230.mission: Commander, I've finished sorting out these tasks. Do look them over.
202230.home: Excellent work. I've prepared a report for you. Take a moment to look it over.
202230.expedition: Commander, the commission is nearly complete. If you head out now, you should be able to meet them as they return.
couple_encourage: Right! Here I go... swiftly!
202230.mail: Commander, you have new mail. Oh, I've been checking about once per hour. So I don't think I've... no, I haven't missed any.
202230.feeling3: Fiji is always telling me to smile more. Is she right? Oh... Sorry, I must be boring you with this...
202230.lose: Sorry. If only I had tried harder...

205070.detail: Dost thy heart cry restlessly in my absence?
205070.touch: The night is both lengthy and brief. Come, blow out the light burning within thee, and accompany me into the dark.
205070.login: O unclean snake, who is it thee lusts after today?
205070.battle: Sinful roses of blood, bloom around me! Bloom!
205070.hp_warning: Perhaps I have indulged myself too much...
205070.feeling2: What a nice gaze. Through thy pupils, I can see another world.
205070.mission_complete: Only the moon and sweet liquor fail to disappoint. We shall share the most unforgettable of nights.
205070.main: The secret behind my battle prowess? Hehe, I sink deeply into visions of the enemy torn from limb to limb. What follows is only natural. |Wales, dost thou intend to hunt the same prey as me? |Please be at ease and close thine eyes. Sink into my embrace, and let thy thoughts flow away.
205070.feeling5: O ignorant snake, hast thou only realised now, how long I have hopelessly been in love with thee? Therefore... would thou give thy everything to me?
205070.upgrade: Did thou hear? A sound that makes my blood boil, like wind passing through the forest in the dead of night.
205070.unlock: I see. So the scent that has been driving me crazy... emanates from thy soul. O sinful Commander who tempts me so, engrave my name upon thine heart - Duke of York, of the Royal Navy.
205070.feeling4: How unfathomable... looking at thy sleeping visage hast made me replete with calmness... Now, pray that thou dost not wake, for I know not what I would do to thee...
205070.feeling1: It would appear... that I must get a little more violent...
205070.propose: Even the most ingenious poet cannot describe the beauty of this moment. Hehe, close thy eyes, feel my warmth, and listen to the beating of my heart. This is the one who shall be thy lifelong partner...
205070.drop_descrip: King George V-class battleship - HMS Duke of York.
205070.skill: All ye, weep at your own demise!
205070.profile: I am King George V-class' Duke of York. Scharnhorst? An interesting one indeed, but now, thou art the one who captures my interest the most... My... if thou displays such an expression to me, I won't be able to contain myself...
205070.touch2: Ahh, how beautiful... thy eyes, normally placid, burning with the fires of lust...
205070.mission: Such fair weather is rare indeed. 'twould be a pity to return to port so soon.
205070.home: Oh, triumphant nightingale that has overcome death itself, what plagues thee enough to silence thy song?
205070.win_mvp: There exists no living being that can resist the embrace of death.
205070.expedition: O mesmerising Narcissus, do remember my warning when greeting those who return. Be misled not by the illusions swirling in the water.
couple_encourage: Karma shall find thee one day.
Stop struggling in futility, my~ little~ kitten~
205070.mail: Thy visage when reading and concentrating, unbudging and focused, resembles one of Michelangelo's sculptures. I do not dislike such determination.
205070.feeling3: How thy visage tempts me so with each passing moment... I must ask of thee, just how sweet is thy blood?
205070.lose: Ahh... why dost thou obstinately refuse to obey me...

305120.detail: Obviously I like being on the center stage with my massive cannons. Performance aside, their size alone boosts morale while intimidating the enemy. You get what I mean, Commander?
305120.touch: Something on your mind? I might be able to help you with it.
305120.login: Look who's finally clocked in, hahahah! My trigger finger's gotten itchy, so let's get on with a sortie already!
305120.battle: Let's duke it out, fair and square!
305120.hp_warning: These guys are tougher than I expected!
305120.feeling2: You okay, Commander? You've had this tired, stiff look on you for a while now... You're not getting rusty like Suruga, are you?
305120.mission_complete: We're wrapping up these missions nicely! Great!
305120.main: Tell me if anyone starts picking on you. I'll put them in their place! And I mean it, for the most part, you hear?|Mmghh! I'm feeling stiff after standing up for so long... What's up, Commander? Why are you blushing? ...My bra's coming off?|Hey, Suruga! What do you say to going drinking with me and the gang once work is done? Figures, always so antisocial... When people invite you, you should go with it!
305120.feeling5: People say you can push yourself harder if it's to protect someone. Then for everyone's sake, I, Kii, shall become the strongest battleship... Pfft, yeah right! Hahahahah!
305120.upgrade: Let's see how strong I've really gotten. Send me into battle!
305120.unlock: Battleship Kii, reporting for duty! Is it true that I'd be able to fight without holding back over here? Heh, good stuff! I look forward to what the future has in store, and you should keep your eyes on me as well!
305120.feeling4: There's no fun in knocking a battle out of the park if nobody's there to witness it. Anyway, once this work is done, I'll go train with Hyuuga. After that, you, I, and Suruga will go for a drink with Ise! Sound good to you?
305120.feeling1: I'm so tired of bosses that can't handle their subordinates, like you.
305120.propose: I mean, we don't need to go that far. We're already dearly important to one another, aren't we? ...Don't worry, I'll still accept it! And of course, I'll keep on keeping you safe, just like I always have!
305120.profile: I am part of the Eighty-Eight Fleet Program: first ship of the Kii-class battleships, Kii. In short, I never got a chance to shine during the war because reasons... But now I have, and I'm going to use it to its fullest! If you have anything that needs doing, just say the word, Commander!
305120.touch2: "Friendly friskiness," is it? Hmm... Sure, I guess?
305120.mission: A new mission? If it's about turning hostiles to scrap, I'll get it done!
305120.home: I reckon we'll garner more fame by winning battles than by wasting time in port, don't you agree?
305120.win_mvp: Victory's ours. Heheh, now that was refreshing all right.
305120.expedition: That last commission was kinda mediocre... Still, they deserve a congratulatory moment. Want to come with me?
couple_encourage: You're the brains, I'm the brawn!
Don't be shy! Let's do this with flair!
Let's celebrate with a glass after we get back!
305120.mail: A letter, eh? If it's an open duel, then I accept their challenge! Oh, no duel, huh...
305120.feeling3: Thought as much. I'll help you with your training, then! Come on, out of your room and into the fresh outdoors for some jogging! And later, we'll do some sparring!
305120.lose: Dammit... Not enough firepower for the job, huh?

105171.detail: Can't take your eyes off me, huh? Nothing wrong with that though~ Just who do you think I am? Ahaha~♪
105171.touch: Your honest feedback, please! Tell me what you really think, okay?
105171.main: Hey, you over there, you're blocking the view! Jeez, I was hoping to treat you to the best seats in the house, Commander.|nil|Keep the spotlight on me! That's right, keep your eyes on the red-hot dance of the Black Dragon, New Jersey!|Being a superstar sure is exciting, isn't it? After all... I didn't come all the way from Planet Bunny for nothing! ...Err, that didn't come across right...|Of course, this dance is something I'd only show you and my closest friends, hehe~|nil
105171.unlock: One, two, jump! Woah, think I nailed it this time~♪ So, how many points would you give me for that? Naturally, a perfect 100, right? Don'tcha just love it when things go smoothly?
105171.drop_descrip: One, two, jump! Woah, think I nailed it this time~♪ So, how many points would you give me for that? Naturally, a perfect 100, right? Don'tcha just love it when things go smoothly?
105171.touch2: I never said you couldn't touch, but... try to mind the time and place, yeah?
105171.home: Shouldn't you be staring at those reports instead of at me? Alright, fine by me. Take a good look at this jump and spin. Oh, you liked that a whole lot, huh?

301150.detail: Stupid Commander! Look at me again and I'll bite you!
301150.touch: Stop touching me! Don't blame me if something blows up!
301150.login: Commander! You're late! Go get ready~ I've been waiting for you.
301150.battle: Let's give a warm welcome to our foolish enemies~!
301150.hp_warning: We're gonna lose? That can't be~!
301150.feeling2: You want good luck? It's not something you can just get.
301150.mission_complete: *Tsk*... If it weren't for the rewards then who'd bother with these jobs...
301150.main: It's so peaceful... How about we play a game of luck?|The gods seem to really love me, so hurry up and shower me with compliments♪|You don't look too good. How about a torpedo to cheer you up?
301150.feeling5: Heheh, silly Commander, you can rely on me as much as you want. I'll do anything you want~! As long as you love me like this, I'm yours♪
301150.upgrade: Mhm, making me stronger is a smart decision.
301150.unlock: I'm {namecode:17}, a {namecode:15}-class destroyer. I don't wanna brag, but I've got the Goddess of Luck watching over me~ Heheh, it's about time people acknowledged that luck is also a part of one's strength♪
301150.feeling4: Getting pranked by me is a lucky thing on its own, you dunce♪ Although I do like that about you.
301150.feeling1: I curse you with bad luck! You idiot!
301150.propose: You just can't be left alone, Commander... Worry not, I will stay by your side and take care of you forever♪
301150.skill: I am {namecode:17} of Sasebo! Watch closely!
301150.profile: I'm {namecode:17}, ship number 2 of the {namecode:15}-class. I worked pretty hard in the First Fleet before I was reassigned to the Second Fleet and participated in the fated Battle of Leyte Gulf... I was the sole survivor, but I'll never forget the bravery everyone showed in that battle... {namecode:79}... {namecode:78}... how I miss you...
301150.touch2: Commander, let's play a game. I'll give you 5 minutes and if you haven't been caught by the police at that point then I'll withdraw my report~
301150.mission: Huh? Work? Geez, it's ALWAYS about work...
301150.win_mvp: That was a good fight, considering how they suck♪
301150.expedition: Hm? Guess it's time. Heheh, I don't even need to actually head out, for as long as I'm in the fleet, bountiful rewards are guaranteed♪
couple_encourage: Monkey Corps {namecode:15}, attack!
Hm? I'm not a monkey?
301150.mail: I brought you your mail~ Now guess which hand I'm holding it with♪
301150.feeling3: Luck comes when you least expect it, you know? For example, like this! (Shigure jumps) ... Commander, maybe you caught a glimpse of my underwear just now~?
301150.lose: N... Not bad... You'd better remember this!

702040.detail: Neither fate nor evil can hamper our ambitions!
702040.login: Good to see you again, Comrade Commander! Let us once more set out to teach our enemy the meaning of unity and solidarity.
702040.hp_warning: No! I am far, far from finished!
702040.feeling2: Never let but's or if's misguide you, Comrade Commander. You alone decide what is right and true.
702040.mission_complete: I knew you would pull through for us, Comrade Commander! Here are the rewards.
702040.main: The strong must always march onward. Holding the line is what the weak do.|Glory is what sustains and strengthens us, and is what will leave our mark on history.|I march onward in the name of a tomorrow where everyone is safe and smiling.
702040.feeling5: To fight not just for your motherland but also for your soulmate, that is what love is... I understand it now. Passion is the fuel of my fighting spirit. And as long as I have you, nothing is impossible!
702040.upgrade: This strength will further our cause!
702040.unlock: I am the child of a union between our unprecedented country and a free spirit! Now, Comrade Commander, let us achieve great things together!
702040.feeling4: I will always watch over you. Should you ever lose your way, I will be the hand that shoves you back on the right path. Only look ahead, never stop advancing!
702040.feeling1: It pains me to say, but I no longer consider you my comrade.
702040.propose: Only a fool chooses between protecting either the world or their lover. There is but one correct answer: protecting them both. We have both the will and the means to do just that. Come, Comrade Commander, let us march onwards!
702040.profile: Salutations, Comrade Commander. I am Kirov. My appearance, rigging, and class are all unimportant in the greater scheme of our ambitions. What matters is that we work together to achieve a future of red glory.
702040.touch2: This is no time for this sort of depravity, Comrade Commander.
702040.mission: It is time to embark on a mission, Comrade Commander.
702040.home: Well fought, Comrade Commander! Your valor warrants the front page spot in the port's newspaper!
702040.win_mvp: Our advance will stop for nothing and nobody!
702040.expedition: A commission has been completed. We must head out and greet the returnees. Our comrades deserve recognition for their efforts.
couple_encourage: Onwards, Northern Parliament comrades!
I have your back,Tallinn!
You may be bourgeois swine... but today, we fight together!
702040.mail: You have mail. Read it through at once. The more comrades, the better. Always.
702040.feeling3: Splendid, Comrade Commander. You've chosen a path of your own. Now follow it and see where it takes you!
702040.lose: Gah...! I cannot and will not succumb until our ambitions have been realized!

301151.detail: You thought I wouldn't bite you just because you complimented my swimsuit? *Hiss*
301151.touch: Don't touch my ears, I'm ticklish there!
301151.battle: Oxygen torpedoes: prepare for simultaneous launch!
301151.main: I'll just absorb some seawater with my tail, and then... Pow! Oh dear~ You're totally drenched, Commander~|{namecode:79} gave me this little rose! If you thought I'd give it to you, think again!|{namecode:79}, just ignore that stupid Commander, come play beach volleyball with me!
301151.unlock: Stupid Commander, I'm not a damn submarine! Do you wanna get hit in the face with an oxygen torpedo?
301151.drop_descrip: Stupid Commander, I'm not a damn submarine! Do you wanna get hit in the face with an oxygen torpedo?
301151.touch2: Wahh! You scared off the fish I'd caught with my tail! Commander, you idiot!

201238.touch: Are you elevating your love for me?
201238.login: Darling~ Where shall we date on this eve?
201238.battle: Come! Raise thine glass to our love!
201238.mission_complete: Mission complete! Next up, dating time~
201238.main: Cleaning is no task for a vampire! We can be lazy every once and a while!|I'm bored... Mine darling, how about a date?|Doth thou beseech the color of mine garmets today? Were thou not the one who dressed me on the morn~
201238.feeling5: I cannot possibly have enough of the time I spend with thee, Commander~ Once thou art done taking thine bath, will thou listen to what I say?
201238.drop_descrip: Those who fall in love with vampires are bound to suffer seven times more than their infatuation. After all, love is a poison which leads to death.
201238.mission: Rather than missions, am I not more important?
201238.home: Darling, what's the souvenir? A test? Could it be a fine wine, or maybe chocolates from a land over yonder?
201238.win_mvp: Flowers and salute fire for my love!
201238.expedition: Oh my darling~ Let us go and greet the maiden's upon thier return~
201238.mail: You want the mail? Then exchange sweet love letters with me~

307100.detail: I would do anything for you, my Commander. Yes, including this "idol" business... Hehehe.
307100.touch: Commander, what are you waiting for? I'm ready for you, anytime, anyplace.
307100.login: Commander, I wonder what's on the schedule for today? Hehehe.
307100.battle: Give my concert your full attention~ Ahahaha!
307100.hp_warning: My love is far stronger than this!
307100.feeling2: Commander, did I hear you want to come see my show? I'm delighted~ Kaga, can you prepare a front row seat?
307100.mission_complete: Mission complete. But I do hope that doesn't mean you will leave my side...?
307100.main: I would like to know~ which girl you cheer for, Commander... I would really, REALLY like to know...|This "idol" business is a little different, but it's no matter. Whatever my Commander wishes of me, I can do...|Kaga, please cancel all of our lessons for the rest of the day. My time with my Commander is so precious, I refuse to waste a single second.
307100.feeling5: You want to get to know the other members? Hmm, if that is what my Commander wishes, I suppose I could accept it... But in return, Commander, you are only allowed to look at me♡
307100.upgrade: Why, this is the strength of my love. Hehehe...
307100.unlock: With the magicks of the Sakura Empire, changing my form like this is a trifle... Hehehe, Commander? Does this Akagi please you?
307100.feeling4: We're at the point now that this group doesn't need any other girls... And I think I need to do a bit of "cleaning" for my Commander... Hehehehe...
307100.feeling1: My Commander's apologetic screams are truly music to my ears... hehehe.
307100.propose: Ahahahaha... all that I am now belongs to my Commander, and everything of my Commander now belongs to me... It will be just like my concerts: your eyes, your ears, even your heart is bound to me... Commander, I will never let you go...
307100.drop_descrip: With the magicks of the Sakura Empire, changing my form like this is a trifle... Hehehe, Commander? Does this Akagi please you?
307100.skill: Ahaha, like dust in the wind.
