307100.profile: Sakura Empire Aircraft Carrier, Akagi, reporting in with a special equipment refit! Commander, things are a little different this time. I'm trying a little "idol" style for you. Won't you please be gentle with me? Hehehehe...
307100.touch2: Don't mind the stares of the spectators in the stands. Take me however you please, my Commander... Hehehe♡
307100.mission: Commander, is there a mission I might help you with?
307100.home: Commander, what would you say to a performance in your honor? Naturally, only Akagi would participate...
307100.win_mvp: Oh my, did I incinerate all those fans clamoring for an encore?
307100.expedition: The meddlesome pests are back... Commander, please excuse me for a moment?
couple_encourage: I work with you out of respect for my Commander.
307100.mail: A letter... Oh, Commander? It couldn't possibly be that you sent a fan letter to another girl...?
307100.feeling3: Commander, if you wish it, I would perform forever for your eyes alone~ Indeed, this stage would belong only to my Commander for the rest of time♡
307100.lose: Gah... that was close. I can't let the Commander see me like this...

202231.detail: Unicorn, this is how you do this problem... Oh sorry, Commander, I'm currently helping the others study. Please make yourself feel at home.
202231.touch: I look cute when wearing glasses...? Err... Um, that wasn't my intention...
202231.login: Good morning. Here is the outline for today's course. Please make sure to review it.
202231.main: Fiji, don't you know that studying is good for you? Come on, Commander, care to back me up on this one? |While I have served as a flagship before, that has nothing to do with what's going on now. I have to be humble and learn from everyone. |I often see Edinburgh in the library. She's always grumbling about what's going on in the maid team or something...
202231.unlock: Commander, why are you here...? Me? Yes, as you can see, I'm still studying... I figured that acquiring knowledge would be the best way to make up for my lack of experience on the actual battlefield.
202231.drop_descrip: Commander, why are you here...? Me? Yes, as you can see, I'm still studying... I figured that acquiring knowledge would be the best way to make up for my lack of experience on the actual battlefield.
202231.touch2: Commander, I d-don't think you should be doing this at school... Ahh!
202231.mail: Commander, you have new mail. I've instructed the Manjuus to help fetch the mail for me even when I can't do it myself, so worry not.

102263.detail: Reno, tired of seeing her commander fighting all alone, assumed an alter ego and joined the commander in the battle against the forces of evil! Pretty cool origin story, wouldn't you say?
102263.touch: This gauntlet I'm always wearing? Oh, uh, I've not made my Reno Bunnino tool belt just yet, so I'm making do with this for now.
102263.login: What can I get you, Commander?
102263.main: So I was telling everyone about Reno Bunnino, and for whatever reason, North Carolina was super keen to hear it... Not like that's a bad thing. More friends is always good!|Hungry, Commander? Vestal taught me a handful of recipes. I could cook something up for you.|Y'know, I think this Reno Bunnino's thing really gonna take off. I'm counting on you to facilitate that, Commander.
102263.unlock: Come on in, Commander! Don't you recognize me? I'm Reno Bunnino – cutesy bunny girl by day, villain-vanquishing superhero by night! Pretty neat concept, am I right?
102263.drop_descrip: Come on in, Commander! Don't you recognize me? I'm Reno Bunnino – cutesy bunny girl by day, villain-vanquishing superhero by night! Pretty neat concept, am I right?
102263.touch2: If you're doing what I think you are... Yeah, sorry, there aren't many clothes my size.
102263.home: When Reno Bunnino's beloved commander comes home to roost, that's her time to shine.

301152.detail: Yamashiro warned me not to pull any weird tricks, and she's treating me like I don't know that already... If anything, she's the one we should worry about...
301152.touch: Look at how you're blushing, Commander! Have you fallen head over heels for me? Heheheh~
301152.login: You came at a good time, Commander! This is where the highlight of the party begins!
301152.main: What's with that spinning gaze of yours? I'm right over here!|What the hell, Yuudachi! At least try to mind your table manners!|There'll be a raffle? Hmph, this time I'll defeat that stupid Yukikaze!
301152.feeling5: I guess I have to always be with you to make sure an idiot like you doesn't get lost♪ Heheh, this beneficiary of Lady Luck will never lose sight of you♪
301152.unlock: Oh my. Commander, you must be pretty lucky to bump into me here, hehe~ Since you're here, you can have the privilege of being my escort tonight. Now, be grateful~♪
301152.drop_descrip: Oh my. Commander, you must be pretty lucky to bump into me here, hehe~ Since you're here, you can have the privilege of being my escort tonight. Now, be grateful~♪
301152.touch2: Eek! Y-you moronic commander! Pay attention to your footwork!
301152.home: H-hey! Don't you leave me hanging over here!

101270.detail: Giiiy... Kiiie... Uh... Bwuuuh...? It's hard to speak like a bunny...
101270.touch: Your hands are so warm, Commander~!
101270.login: Are you feeling good today, Commander? Let me inject some bunny power into you!
101270.feeling2: I'll do my best, even though I'm just a bunny!
101270.mission_complete: Look, Commander! I brought the rewards we got! Aren't I great~?
101270.main: The most delish carrot is always going to be the next one!|I've received a transmission from Planet Bunny telling me to help you with your work. No need to thank me, just leave it to me!|I'm going to become a superstar one day! The most popular in the universe!
101270.feeling5: My sister told me that bunnies die if they get too lonely! That's why I came to see you~! Do you... not want to visit me, Commander?
101270.upgrade: My bunny level has gone up even higher! Yeah!
101270.unlock: I'm Bailey, a Benson-cla... Wait, no, I'm a bunny! Commander, have you seen any of my sisters?
101270.feeling4: C'mon, Commander, play with me~! Busy with work? Hehe, look again, Commander. No need to thank me!
101270.feeling1: You're the enemy of the bunnies, Commander!
101270.propose: Pro...mise? Promise what? I don't really get it. Do you wanna become a bunny too? ... Great! That means we can be together forever!
101270.drop_descrip: Benson-class Destroyer - Bailey, Hull Number DD-492!
101270.skill: Here I go! Bunny Boosted Bane Blaster!
101270.profile: I'm from Planet Bunny. I'm a bunny, just like my sisters! I'm super good at giving providing fire support. I've even earned awards for it, believe it or not! Hehe, I'm super strong!
101270.mission: You should definitely stock up on carrots, but you shouldn't stock up on unfinished missions!
101270.home: Good work, Commander! Want to try some of my handmade cookies?
101270.win_mvp: Haha! Bunnies are just super strong!
101270.expedition: Commander, the girls who were out on a commission have returned! Let's give them a warm welcome! If we don't have regular exercise then we'll start to rust!
101270.mail: Commander, new mail arrived! Is it from Planet Bunny?
101270.feeling3: Benson told me that I'm from Planet Bunny... Does she think I'm still a kid or something? But... but... I know for a fact that Santa is real!
101270.lose: *Sob*... Planet Bunny won't let you off so easily!

201099.touch: Commander, are you scared? Since there's no helping it, you can hold onto my hand.
201099.main: O-of course! As a full-fledged lady, you can trust me with anything! |Shouldn't you give a cute lady like me some preferential treatment? |Comet, dump that stupid commander and let me be your manager!
201099.unlock: Cute? Pretty? Is that all? Can't you expand your vocabulary a little? Jeez... Commander, you really should learn to whisper sweet nothings into my ear!
201099.drop_descrip: Cute? Pretty? Is that all? Can't you expand your vocabulary a little? Jeez... Commander, you really should learn to whisper sweet nothings into my ear!
201099.touch2: Stupid Commander! The standard for maturity isn't one's size!

107080.detail: Limbs... cams... stabilisers... hmm? Commander, do you require something? I'm quite busy with the inspection, so do as you like~
107080.touch: Zipper? Hehe, please don’t mind me. This is just more convenient for me to move around~
107080.login: Commander, remember to knock before you open the door next time. Otherwise, I can’t guarantee that I won’t accidentally shoot you...
107080.battle: Let me give you a taste of my Wasp battle style!
107080.feeling2: I like natural but in actuality use a compound bow? Commander, you are stereotyping, this is called going with the times! And the use of a compound bow actually has a long history to it. You can listen to me tell you it all, in ancient times...
107080.mission_complete: Commander, come over here and take your rewards from the mission~ It’s too heavy for me to shoot it at you...
107080.main: Commander, where are you looking at, I am above you. Hahaha, indoor climbing is quite interesting~ | It’s said that the archers of Sakura Empire is totally different from mine. So I really want to see it. | Commander, if there’s nothing I can help with then I’ll go out and exercise?
107080.feeling5: Archery, combat techniques, and… that sea of stars night, this is all I have. Commander, are you willing to accept me as who I am?
107080.upgrade: Oh, my physical strength has grown stronger, it's time to customize my bow.
107080.unlock: Hmm? So you are the so-called Commander? Ok... if there is enough room in your fleet, then is it alright for me join you~
107080.feeling4: Commander, let me teach you archery. At night, we can practice together. If you get tired, then we can stargaze. How does that sound?
107080.feeling1: If you don’t want to get shot by me, then just stay away...
107080.propose: Is this your answer, Commander? … hehehe, I am so very happy! Then—— “I am willing to give everything to you, my dearest Commander”—— Wow, I’m so shy,  i-isn’t this awkward?
107080.drop_descrip: Wasp class aircraft carrier- Wasp, hull number CV-7.
107080.skill: Who said a wasp can only sting once?
107080.profile: I am Wasp class carrier, Wasp~! The first thing I did was go on missions in the Atlantic, and I also supported the Royal Navy. Later on, when in the thick of things in the Pacific theater, I was sent to support my Yorktown sisters. But in the end, I didn’t help quite as much. After all, I was most afraid of torpedoes...
107080.touch2: Commander, say the word, where do you NOT want to get shot at? I’ll try to avoid it~
107080.mission: Commander, we have a new mission. You can give me an errand or a target. But please no paperwork~
107080.home: Commander, what do you think, the outdoors is more comfortable, right?
107080.win_mvp: Hehe, I am very good, right?
107080.expedition: The commission fleet has returned, that’s good to hear. I also want to head out... Co-man-der~
107080.mail: Commander, did you get the letter I just shot to you from outside?
107080.feeling3: Someone saw a ghost on the roof last night? Hahaha, that was probably me practicing outdoors~ It’s very comfortable at night, no one bothers you, and you’re surrounded by stars. Commander, you want to come try?
107080.lose: Umm... it seems that today’s status is not very good...

701060.detail: Everyone in the Northern Parliament likes calling each other "comrade." Comrade Commander! I'm Comrade Stremitelny! ...Buuuut, that's a heck of a mouthful, so I'm just gonna call you Commander!
701060.touch: Do you like playing with snowballs too?
701060.login: Hurry up and come play in the snow with me!
701060.hp_warning: I hate airplanes! Shoo, go away!
701060.feeling2: My snowballs are gentle! There are no rocks or bits of ice inside, only softness!
701060.headtouch: Geh, you meanie! You're gonna make my hat come off!
701060.main: Chang Chun and I were looking into a way to retrofit our naval guns into snowball launchers. Eh, that's not allowed..?|Why am I called Snezhok? Well, it means "Little Snowball," and I'm a little cutie who likes snowballs.|During the winter, you can have snowball fights, build snowmen, and wear fuzzy clothing! Winter's the best!
701060.feeling5: Come build snowmen with me, Commander! You'll make one, I'll make one, and then we can have them hold hands, just like we're doing now! Ehehe~
701060.upgrade: Snowball fight or gunfight, I feel like I can't lose!
701060.unlock: Way! Too! Slow! Why'd it take you so long to find me?! That's right! I'm Stremitelny of the Gnevny class, but you can also call me by my nickname, Snezhok! Anyway, here's a snowball to commemorate our meeting, catch~!
701060.feeling4: Are you cold, Commander? C'mere! Come stick your hands here where it's nice and fluffy! ...Hehe, aren't I super nice?
701060.feeling1: I hate you! Stay away! One step closer and I'm gonna pummel you with snowballs!
701060.propose: Hauuu... My face is burning hot, like I'm gonna melt for real! But... if I can melt right into your heart like this... that wouldn't be half bad. Ehehe~
701060.profile: So, I'm Stremitelny of the Gnevny class. My friends and I did some escort missions as well as coastal support operations! Commander, if there's anything I can help with, just say the word!
701060.touch2: Now I'm angry! Take this! And this! And this!
701060.mission: Commander, are you letting your missions pile up like snow on the branches?
701060.home: My sisters said that I'm not allowed to drink vodka because that stuff melts snowballs or something... Uhh, somehow that doesn't sound quite right...
701060.win_mvp: Hehe, victory! Commander, I want a prize!
701060.expedition: I'll go greet the friends coming back from their commission! ...I'm not going to throw snowballs at them!
couple_encourage: C'mon, just give me a little taste!
701060.mail: Your mail's here! Catch~! ...Eh, I'm not allowed to throw it...?
701060.feeling3: Secret technique! Snow down the back of your neck! That oughta freshen you back up, or so Minsk said! ...Um, Commander... You're not upset, are you?

303130.detail: Would you stop staring at me like that? I can't promise my sword won't come your way...
303130.touch: Commander, you’re getting on my nerves.
303130.login: Commander, you want someone like me to keep you company today as well? What a strange person...
303130.feeling2: Didn’t I already tell you? Don’t talk to me if you don’t have any business.
303130.mission_complete: Mission complete... Can I go back now?
303130.main: We were doomed to stray from the path of righteousness the moment we took up arms. Commander, we can never become heroes.|The South, Solomon Island, Leyte Gulf, and now this sea... Nothing ever changes...|Being by Yamato is like a warm embrace that melts away my worries... I sometimes long for that feeling... N-no, it’s not Iike that! I may have said that but, not in that way! But if I put it that way...
303130.feeling5: My dream is to one day conquer the sky and everything beneath it. When that day comes, would you still remain by my side?
303130.upgrade: Strength may breed sin, but for now, we have no other choice.
303130.unlock: I'm {namecode:68}, the one who will tear open the sky. You're the Commander...? Don't get too close... You might get hurt!
303130.feeling4: Commander, you sure are a strange person. I’ve never felt anything like this before... but it’s not all that bad. Hey, care to have a little chat with me?
303130.feeling1: If you get too close to me, I’ll cut you down
303130.propose: I’m not very good at expressing my emotions... but despite that, you’ve never left my side. As long as you’re willing to call for me, I will be able to continue fighting. Commander... I don’t want to let go of your hand.
303130.drop_descrip: Third ship of the {namecode:66}-class heavy cruisers, {namecode:68}.
303130.profile: {namecode:68}, third ship of the {namecode:66}-class. My little sister and I are twins, but we're a good bit younger than our older sisters... Feel free to leave both the enemies in the sky and on the sea to me. You'll need to deal with those underwater yourself. And one final reminder: don't get too close to me or you might get hurt!
303130.touch2: Stand still over there. I want to practice my swordsmanship.
303130.home: Combat operations over... Seems like we didn't encounter any worthy opponents today... again...
303130.win_mvp: I shall slay anything that stands in my way, whether ghost or god!
303130.feeling3: I said don’t talk to me if-... You want to know more about me? Fine... as you wish.
303130.lose: ... It hurts... No, don't mind me.

205072.detail: Ahaha... I can hear the beating of thy heart. Yes, throb, throb... Ahh, what an enrapturing sound...
205072.touch: Dost thou intend to spend the night alone, or perhaps... wouldst thou like to partake of a drink with me?
205072.login: Dost thou wish to try this blood... coloured fruity beverage?
205072.main: Thou need not be nervous. This attire is but a temporary one... Perhaps thou believed to have escaped from my usual self? Ahaha... |Even though a night eternal may be out of the question, dost thou not wish... to sink into the embrace of night with me? |Following thy ideals are akin to swimming endlessly against the current... However, the way thou refuseth to bow thy head before fate gives me ample reason to remain by thee. Hehe...

301160.feeling5: A wedding dress? So, have you finally started thinking about your eternity of servitude to Yukikaze the Great? Well, you have good taste... Huh? This is for someone else? W-wait... wait... please, I know I'm not perfect, but... Huh? A friend's wedding ceremony? You big jerk!!!
301160.upgrade: So you've noticed Yukikaze's greatness? You have good eyes~
301160.unlock: Hehehe~ As a reward for making it this far, the lucky Yukikaze the Great shall join you! You should feel honored!
301160.feeling4: You want to go out with me? Hmph! There's no way the elegant and beautiful Yukikaze would just accept the advances of any random person... W-wait!! Are you seriously going to leave before I have a chance to collect my thoughts?!
301160.feeling1: You are not worthy of the luck of Yukikaze the Great~
301160.propose: Since you asked so earnestly, Yukikaze the Great shall grant you a favor and allow you to carry her! Come on, what are you waiting for? It's a once in a lifetime opportunity!
301160.profile: Listen up! I'm the noble, lucky, invincible, magni... magnici... the 8th ship of the Kagerou-class, Yukikaze the Great! What the heck... that word's so hard to pronounce... Ahem! Anyway, I shall be your lucky star from now on, so be grateful! Wa ha ha!
301160.touch2: What are... you doing... nngh!? Go die!!
301160.mission: How naïve, Commander! You still have tasks left to do!
301160.home: You were only able to return safely because of my luck, so be thankful!
301160.win_mvp: Losers should hurry up and scram! Wa ha ha!
301160.expedition: Woof! Are you sure that barking increases the likelihood of getting a better reward...?
301160.mail: Here's your mail... Grrrr, even more popular than me...
301160.feeling3: You'd like to go to an amusement park with Yukikaze the Great? Hmph! There's no way that I'd do something so childish... Ahh! W-wait, let's talk this over! I'm sure there's some fun to be had at an amusement park!
301160.lose: Hmph. I don't want anyone finding out that I lost, so I'm letting you go this time!

701041.detail: Dear comrade, how long are you going to keep me like this? ...Is that so... Ehh? Forever?!
701041.login: Dear comrade, do you really think you can keep me bound like this? ...Is that so? Naive fool. Hehe~
701041.main: I knew there was something... wrong about that chocolate... I never thought this would happen to me... my head's still spinning... |When I was talking to Zara, she said I look more appealing in this outfit. So... what do you think, dear comrade? |I'm not like Avrora. I can't drink at all... Ah, wait, I'm not talking about vodka!
701041.unlock: ...*Sigh*, I never thought I'd get captured by these little guys... Dear comrade, does Tashkent really have to play along with this?
701041.drop_descrip: ...*Sigh*, I never thought I'd get captured by these little guys... Dear comrade, does Tashkent really have to play along with this?
701041.touch2: Wait, I'm not okay with this role reversal! I should be the one touching you, dear comrade!
701041.home: Welcome back. We're all throwing a big party tonight. ...I'm not lying! I'm going to invite everyone from the Northern Parliament over!
701041.win_mvp: Heheh, not a bad display of power, right?
701041.expedition: You can't lift the mission rewards? ...Is that so? What a wimp. Here, I'll do it for you. I can leave it over here, right?

201103.detail: Comet and Crescent picked this outfit for me, but... ain't it a bit too showy? Erm... it's too much, innit? Um... n-never mind!
201103.touch: Hold your hand so I don't get lost?! Erm, um, uh, I think holdin' your sleeve's good enough, Commandeeer...!
201103.login: There you are, Commander! I was worried ya lost me...
201103.main: It's so cold I'd rather stay inside and eat fish and chips come wintertime... But goin' out with you's pretty nice too!|Commander, I heard there's gonna be one of them fireworks shows for New Year's! What say we go together?|Commander, umm... what do ya think of me, Comet, and Crescent doin' like a New Year's concert for ya all dressed up like this in Sakura Empire clothes?
201103.feeling5: My New Year's wish? Oh, I got lots... Let's see... I hope everyone in the fleet stays safe. And I hope I can become a big, famous idol... And, Commander, I hope you'll be there with me the whole way...
201103.unlock: Aww... it took me a while to get changed... Hope I didn't keep ya waitin' too long, Commander? Hehe... th-that's good. Let's get goin', then~
201103.drop_descrip: Aww... it took me a while to get changed... Commander, did I keep you waiting long? Hehe... th-that's good. Let's get going, then~
201103.home: Here, Commander, I got ya some fish and chips... Oh, was I supposed to give ya mochi for New Year's instead?

103250.detail: A spin there... backstep there! Whew... Yeah, I'm just working out the choreography for our new single. Gotta come up with something everyone in the troop can dance, not just me.
103250.touch: How's this for a signature pose? Good?
103250.login: What's on our schedule today, Commander? Same as always, I'm counting on you.
103250.battle: Just an idol, passing by... Nah, that just sounds off. Anyway, let's do this!
103250.hp_warning: A small screwup isn't gonna stop me!
103250.feeling2: Your job is to plan our schedule, and our job is to follow it. So business as usual, I guess, huh? Hahahah!
103250.mission_complete: Got some mission rewards here. Oh, and I got rid of that trap Albacore set.
103250.main: There's tons of idol business to tend to, so I've not had much time to help people. Think you pick up the mantle for a while, Commander? Thanks, you're a hero! Hahahah!|These moves might be too hard for the Royal Navy girls... What do you think, Commander?|Th-this whole "cute" thing isn't exactly my thing... N-not that I hate it, and YOU seem to like it, I guess... Ughh...
103250.feeling5: You think I am cute? Especially when my eyes are on you? A-alright then... Now I know not to give up! This might be selfish to ask, but do you think we could do some special training together, so I can truly shine on stage?
103250.upgrade: Thanks a bunch. Guess I should say: look forward to our next performance!
103250.unlock: The name's Baltimore, Eagle Union heavy cruiser. Whoops, right, I'm not just a soldier anymore, but an idol as well. I agreed to do it, and I'm gonna do it as best I can. We'll be counting on your support, Commander.
103250.feeling4: "Thanks for supporting me!" ...Yeah, Bremerton's right, my delivery is just a bit off... Hey, Commander, do I fit in with the other members? Am I really... cute?
103250.feeling1: A control freak like you isn't fit to instruct us. Loosen up a bit, then try again.
103250.propose: This I promise you, Commander: we'll all work together to bring you the best performance ever! In return I ask for one thing: that you witness it, and witness me, at my cutest.
103250.drop_descrip: The name's Baltimore, Eagle Union heavy cruiser. Whoops, right, I'm not just a soldier anymore, but an idol as well. I agreed to do it, and I'm gonna do it as best I can. We'll be counting on your support, Commander.
103250.skill: Far and near! Hear our song loud and clear!
103250.profile: Heavy cruiser Baltimore, currently serving as an idol to test the Muse System. I'm giving it my all to put on the best performance you'll ever see.
103250.mission: Mission time, eh... You're really not in an enviable position, having to keep doing those while we work as idols.
103250.home: Oh, you're back. Hope everyone else made it safe and sound too. An idol needs an audience, after all.
103250.win_mvp: Picking me was the right choice, am I right? I'm never gonna let you down.
103250.expedition: Commission complete! What do you say we welcome them back with a small performance?
couple_encourage: Together now! In formation, on standby!
103250.mail: Thanks, Dido, I really appreciate it. Got a letter for you here, Commander.
103250.feeling3: How do I look, Commander? This outfit's more revealing than what I'm used to... D-does it really make me look cuter?
103250.lose: Looks like we need to rehearse it from the top...

301161.detail: Even though this dress perfectly suits Yukikaze the Great, it makes it hard to play on the swings... Urgh... what should I do?!
301161.touch: Yes, yes! That's right, Commander, put your back into it! Wa ha haaaahh!! I'm flyingggg~!
301161.login: Commander, good timing! I shall allow you to help push my swing!
301161.battle: You thought this was just a regular swing set, but behold! Torpedo tubes!
301161.main: Ahh, I can feel Commander's longing gazes... but alas! This swing set is for Yukikaze the Great, and no one else! Wa ha ha! Am I not downright evil? |My gothic dress? Heheh~ You might think I've gotten tired of hearing it, but... I shall allow you to praise the beauty of Yukikaze the Great! Haha! |Swinging around too much shakes around your brain and makes you stupid...? And the only way to fix it is to stay in one spot and work? Really?! Um, I suppose... it can't be helped then...
301161.unlock: Wa ha ha! My "universal-as-long-as-there-is-a-ceiling" swing set is finally complete! Commander, are you jealous? Want to give it a try? Too~ bad~! This seat is reserved only for the noble and elegant Yukikaze!
301161.drop_descrip: Wa ha ha! My "universal-as-long-as-there-is-a-ceiling" swing set is finally complete! Commander, are you jealous? Want to give it a try? Too~ bad~! This seat is reserved only for the noble and elegant Yukikaze!
301161.touch2: Funyaaaagh! Th-that scared me half to death!! Dumb Commander, go die already!
301161.win_mvp: If you think Yukikaze the Great is simply here for fun and games, you'd be dead wrong!

702030.detail: Commander, let's chat a bit? It's important that we get to know each other... don't you think?
702030.touch: You want to feel? Ah, not this little guy. I mean me. Hehehe.
702030.login: Welcome, Commander. So this is your office...? Aha, of course, it's OUR office, isn't it?
702030.battle: I can handle these girls just fine! Hiyah!
702030.feeling2: Commander, did you have something to talk about? Or are you just here for a little chat? With this fleet, we could go on and on. Hehehe.
702030.mission_complete: Wow, you completed that mission all by yourself! Hehe, were you hoping I'd give you a reward?
702030.main: Are you jealous of my little friend here, Commander...? Oh, you're not? Hmm.|I'm actually very strong... Or at least, I was designed to be. I guess I would need you to check and make sure I actually turned out that way, Commander.|If you're worried those you trust will betray you, you just have to keep them close. Either rope or chains will do the trick... right?
702030.feeling5: Oh my... that looks serious. You really do need someone you love and cherish by your side... Commander, let me be here for you. I'll take care of all your worries for you.
702030.upgrade: Keep strengthening my equipment. I know you can do it.
702030.unlock: So you're the Commander? Hehe, I like what I see... Ah, excuse me. I'm Chapayev, a light cruiser from the Northern Parliament. Let's get along~
702030.feeling4: A pet? I wonder... I've never had one before. The one I love and cherish is always right here with me, after all. Say, Commander... Do you need more affection?
702030.feeling1: You may need some stricter training. Hm. Worrying...
702030.propose: To get such a ring... such a beautiful gift, it's wonderful. So let me give you this bridle in return... Hehe, it fits perfectly. Now it's like we're always connected, wherever we might be... Don't you love it?
702030.profile: I am the name ship of Project 68-K, also known as the Chapayev-class. I was meant to participate in the war, but due to a series of delays, I was not completed in time. I didn't really do anything. Too bad. Hehehe.
702030.mission: All these unfinished tasks... Wouldn't it be better if I helped you take care of them?
702030.home: What do you think of my food? Is this the kind of thing you like to eat?
702030.expedition: Commander, the girls you sent out on commission are back. Are you ready?
702030.mail: I sorted the mail for you. Don't forget to look it over.
702030.feeling3: Fraternizing with subordinates...? Yes, these among comrades who put our lives in each other's hands, trust is the most important thing. I hope you trust in me, Commander, the same way I trust in you.

702029.detail: Now with my modernization upgrades, I can give other ships a run for their money! Don'tcha think I deserve a lot more respect for all my potential, experience, and charm~?
702029.login: Yoohoo~♪ Remember to keep your nose to the grindstone for adorable old me~
702029.main: Oof, my shoulders feel so stiff~! Let me just give my arms a good stretch and shake my butt to get my circulation going~ Oh~? What're you eyeing me for~?|Listen, darling, I could really go for some Dragon Empery-style fried rice! Yeah, you guessed right— go buy me some takeout~♪|nil
702029.unlock: My retrofitting is done! Look forward to seeing how both my cuteness and combat potential have been upgraded!
702029.drop_descrip: My retrofitting is done! Look forward to seeing how both my cuteness and combat potential has been upgraded!
702029.touch2: I keep it fairly tight, if you know what I mean~
702029.win_mvp: You thought an old ship couldn't whoop your asses? Loooosers~♪
702029.lose: Owww, my back... That proves it, I'm not fit for these exhausting battles!

601021.touch: Commander! Err, I mean, good day?

601021.main: If you're thirsty, I brought some water. Here you go! |The warm sunlight, the gentle breeze, and an ice pop to beat the heat! That's the spirit of midsummer! |Commander, I heard from a friend that all girls have multiple facets... When I changed into this outfit that I'd absolutely never wear normally... it, it was as if something awakened within me...
601021.feeling5: I once said I wanted to be your bodyguard, but when we're walking together like this, it feels like you're guarding me instead. Would this be dereliction of duty...? Ah! I wasn't saying that I disapproved of it! *sigh*...
601021.unlock: Lady Veneto advised me to enjoy my time off by changing into something befitting the occasion... Um, Commander, I d-don't look strange, do I?
601021.drop_descrip: Lady Veneto advised me to enjoy my time off by changing into something befitting the occasion... Um, Commander, I d-don't look strange, do I?
601021.mission: Wouldn't it be better to finish the missions first...
601021.lose: Ugh... I s-suppose I'm not cut out for this after all...

702032.touch: Do you want me to oil you up?
702032.login: Welcome, Commander. Working today, like always? Well, keep at it.
702032.main: Mmmgh~ You ought to stretch a little, Commander. Sitting down all the time leads to back and shoulder problems, and all other sorts of bad things.|This book? I picked it up on Belorussiya's recommendation. It might be a bit too hard for you, though. ...Unlikely, you say? Read me a few pages, then.|There we go... This lotion is sticky, but it's good for the skin. You should get into the habit of using skincare products too, Commander.
702032.unlock: Phew... Oh my, Commander, I'm sorry I didn't welcome you at the door. You don't have to be so tense - I already know not to try doing anything weird with you. Hehe~
702032.drop_descrip: Phew... Oh my, Commander, I'm sorry I didn't welcome you at the door. You don't have to be so tense - I already know not to try doing anything weird with you. Hehe~
702032.touch2: Heehee, I might have used too much lotion.
702032.home: You must be tired. How about a sweet refreshment to clear away the fatigue? Here you are, sweetheart. Just don't have too much, now.

301651.detail: The butterflies go fluttering by~♪ Oh, the Manjuus are also chasing after the butterflies.
301651.touch: You want to see me spin around? Spiiiin, spiiiin~♪
301651.login: Commander, would you like to take a stroll? There are cute little butterflies in this garden~
301651.main: Ooshio looks very mature in her dress, doesn't she~ It's a bit too soon for me still, right?|These balloons? I got them from Ariake. She brought a bunch just for the occasion; isn't that amaaazing?|It's so nice throwing a party in nice and warm weather! Commander, do you prefer this, or a fancy banquet?
301651.unlock: Hello, Commander. Oh, you think I look good in this fluttery dress~? Thank you very much!
301651.drop_descrip: Hello, Commander. Oh, you think I look good in this fluttery dress~? Thank you very much!
301651.touch2: Eep! Commander, my tail's all tickly~
301651.home: I'm glad I came along with my sisters~

202221.touch: For a Royal maid like myself to don the attire of the Dragon Empery... isn't this what cultural exchange is all about?
202221.login: Welcome back, Commander. Today, I'll be visiting the girls from the Dragon Empery to learn a bit more about their customs. Would you like to come with me?
202221.main: Commander, even if you're just eating a pork bun, please make sure to use a serviette. |Etiquette is closely linked to culture, so it's no surprise that there are many differences between the Royal Navy and the Dragon Empery. |The girls from the Empery said that they'd be willing to teach me a few New Year's greetings. Once I've learned them, I'll be able to give you some blessings!
202221.unlock: You can feel the profound heritage and culture of the Dragon Empery from all these customs and outfits for the Lunar New Year's Festival… It seems to be ever more necessary to study the traditions and etiquette of this wondrous culture.
202221.drop_descrip: You can feel the profound heritage and culture of the Dragon Empery from all these customs and outfits for the Lunar New Year's Festival… It seems to be ever more necessary to study the traditions and etiquette of this wondrous culture.
202221.home: Good work, Commander. Today, would you like to try some tea from the Dragon Empery?

307121.detail: You came here looking for someone to talk to, right? I suppose I can keep you company then, but you should make sure you go around and deepen your bonds with everyone else too! ...Except Junyou, watch out for that one!
307121.login: Hellooooo, Commander! Are we starting work today with some of that festive spirit? I didn't just bring my festive spirit with me today, I came ready with the whole package, outfit and all! I'll be happy as long as you can feel that holiday cheer~!
307121.mission_complete: Excellent! With these earnings, we'll be able to eat as much as we want... Well yeah, I know that! We need to share with everyone else too! ...B-but, I'd be really happy if you treated me to a little something... Please?
307121.main: When the fireworks climb high into the sky and go "kaboom," I can feel my excitement doing the very same thing! Ahahaha!|Commander, are you totally into my getup? You are, aren't you! Aha, I totally knew it! Come and feast your eyes all you want then~♪|nil
307121.unlock: It's– summer– festival– time–!! Uhh, well, maybe it's a bit too late for a "summer" festival, so maybe a regular festival is fine? Well, the important thing is that you have lots of fun, Commander! Because I sure as heck will!
307121.drop_descrip: It's– summer– festival– time–!! Uhh, well, maybe it's a bit too late for a "summer" festival, so maybe a regular festival is fine? Well, the important thing is that you have lots of fun, Commander! Because I sure as heck will!
307121.mission: Missions? Can't you let it rest for a day and just enjoy the day off??
307121.home: Woohoo, you're back, Commander! Bring any goodies back for me and the girls? I'm already so excited I can't calm down!
307121.win_mvp: Victory is mine! That's how a real carrier does things, duh!

701040.detail: Did you come to watch me practice? ...So, are you staying or what?
701040.touch: What is it? Oh, you have work for me? Is that so... Fine, I'll take care of it.
701040.login: Is it that fun staring at Tashkent? ...Is that so? Well, do as you please.
701040.battle: Let's beat them to a pulp! Ура!
701040.feeling2: Do you need me for anything, dear comrade? I'm busy, so make it quick... Oh, is that so...? You just wanted to play? Well, I suppose I have some time to burn, so...
701040.mission_complete: Mission rewards, huh... Lemme take a look. So...? Is there any food?
701040.main: I was born in Sardegna, so I'm quite familiar with their cuisine. Well, it's not like it matters if the people here like that kind of food. |Why is so g'damn hot here? Dear comrade, go turn the air conditioning on for me?♡ |How strange... It's not like I make any effort to be friendly or sociable, so why do people end up liking me more? Hey, do you know why that might be, dear comrade?
701040.feeling5: I don't really know anyone here, but everyone seems to genuinely like me. That's even after knowing what kind of person I am, so I want to be better. Of course I feel the same way about you, dear comrade. After all, I like you!
701040.upgrade: It's my turn to fight? ...Is that so? Fine, I'll do it.
701040.unlock: I'm Tashkent. Some call me the Blue Cruiser. Another comrade who wants to woo me? It's just about recruitment...? I see. What a hopeless fellow you are.
701040.feeling4: I'm just a normal girl. I don't want special treatment or anything. The same goes for you, dear comrade, I'm sure of it...
701040.propose: So, this was the important thing you were telling me about? ...Sure, I'll take it. ...What, didn't I already tell you before that I like you? So, nothing wrong with us getting married, right?
701040.skill: I'll have you witness my true power!
701040.profile: I'm Tashkent, flotilla leader destroyer from the Northern Parliament. There are three other... actually, nevermind. I'm called the "Blue Cruiser" because of my Sardegna-style construction. Of course, I'm a destroyer, and I have nothing against that. I'll put up results just like I did during the Battle of Sevastopol, so look forward to it.
701040.touch2: Eh...? What are you trying to do? Are the puffy balls on my outfit that interesting?
701040.mission: Missions? Is there anything that looks interesting?
701040.home: Welcome back. ...Tea? Nah, I have vodka though.
701040.win_mvp: Ура! Did you witness my true power!
701040.expedition: Dear comrade, did you forget about the commissions? Are you dumb? Even I remembered.
couple_encourage: Unlike you, I don't have anyone to enjoy Sardegnian cooking with...
When we get serious, nothing can keep us down!
701040.mail: I brought the mail. You don't have to thank me for it or anything.
701040.feeling3: With a nickname like "the Blue Cruiser," you'd expect me to be someone who's cute and well-behaved right? People are always disillusioned as all hell after meeting me... and, well, I can't blame them. What do you think, dear comrade?

106020.detail: Please keep my stats in mind!
106020.touch: What's this? Training to resist against attacks?
106020.login: The best pitchers are always training. Yep!
106020.feeling2: Someday, I hope to stand on the podium of the sea with your lead!
106020.mission_complete: It's satisfying to be rewarded for achieving the objective! Commander, check out the rewards!
106020.main: With this ball, I can sink a submarine!|Commander, can you polish the B-25s?|Boring... You look tired anyway, Commander, so let's go and sink some subs?
106020.feeling5: Co-Commander. If I win in the next league, I- I'll tell you something important! S- So please wait for it! I will become stronger. Stronger than anyone!
106020.upgrade: My balls have become even faster!
106020.unlock: *inhale*...HAA! Nice one... Oh, apologies. You're the Commander, I see. Fast pitcher, Bogue, here for duty!
106020.feeling4: Commander! I, Bogue, am requesting special training! The reason is, whenever I hear your voice, I lose my strength so I want to know how to prevent that... That's all!
106020.feeling1: Can you really make me stronger, Commander? ...I'm really worried...
106020.propose: ...Now I understand! You noticed my feelings, Commander, and you want me to continue my journey without regrets! I, Bogue, am truly happy to have met you!
106020.drop_descrip: Bogue-class escort carrier — Bogue, Hull Number CVE-9!
106020.profile: I am pro baseballer, Bogue! Yep, my greatest record is 12 strikeouts in a single match! I wish to sharpen my skills by your side, and become the shining star of the Major League!
106020.mission: A new goal? I will not back down!
106020.home: Commander, you are a real veteran! That was a learning experience!
106020.win_mvp: Hmhmm~ As I thought, I am the best pitcher.
106020.expedition: Curveball~! Oh crap I broke the window... Ah, Commander, the commission squad is back!
106020.mail: Commander, it's a mail! Which championship is it from?
106020.feeling3: You always give me the right ideas, Commander! As expected of a great coach! I, Bogue the pitcher, will follow you for life!
106020.lose: Is this the end of the tournament...?

101265.drop_descrip: Eldridge, arriving at designated altitude... Moon, mooncake, and Manjuus spotted...

307120.detail: If you want to keep me company so badly... Well, I just happened to not have anyone to talk to, so you'll have to make do! In any case, let me start by telling you about my favorite kind of azalea––
307120.touch: What's the matter? Oh, you need me for something? Well, seeing how earnestly you're beseeching my aid, I have no choice but to at least consider it~
307120.login: Hello there, Commander! Today's workload is looking a bit heavy and I wonder if we might have to do some overtime but I'm sure if we get right down to business we'll be able to finish– Commander??
307120.battle: Harrumph! With me at helm, victory is already assured!
307120.hp_warning: Are you really going to let your all-important aircraft carrier get hit like this?!
307120.feeling2: How many times have I had to explain this to you before? I can do everything that an aircraft carrier is supposed to do, but I can't do anything outside of that because that's just what I used to be!
307120.headtouch: You think you can mess with my heart just by patting my head? How naive! ...If you remember to keep it up 365 days of the year, maybe you'll have a shot.
307120.mission_complete: Quite satisfactory! With such abundant rewards, you'll be able to further expand your scope of work and have even more missions assigned to you! But... Hehe, are you able to shoulder that immense workload?
307120.main: Skip bombing? I must admit, it was quite an imaginative tactic. The Eagle Union was even able to give one as cute and strong as me a headache! Ahahaha!|If you're tired, just let me handle the paperwork. Nobody would notice the difference if I forged your signature... Ah, uh, that was obviously just a joke!|I left half a cake for you on your desk. Why only half, you ask? Well, that's because... I already ate the other half! Ahahaha!
307120.feeling5: You know how in those books, if there's someone on your mind, it normally goes something like "your face gets all red and you can't find the words to say?" But, like, in my case, I just can't stop talking at all... Ah! I get it now! I'm not the one who's nervous, you are! ...Hey, are you listening to me?
307120.upgrade: Mhm, that's more like it! I'll offer you some words of praise for recognizing my worth!
307120.unlock: Hello there, Commander! I'm the Unryuu-class aircraft carrier, Katsuragi. I'm not just a carrier, I'm a full-fledged aircraft carrier, meaning that I can do everything that an aircraft carrier is supposed to do! I'm not telling ya what I don't like, but as for hobbies, I've got a whole buncha those~ For example... (1 minute later) ...So yeah! Hey, Commander, are you still listening?
307120.feeling4: Commander! I happened to discover something amazing! Tomorrow is a holiday, and there aren't many days like it, and by pure "coincidence," neither you or I have anything to do! So basically, I was thinking, what could the two of us do on such a rare and special day when we have nothing else to do? Haah, there are too many possibilities~!
307120.feeling1: This simply won't do, Commander... I had no idea that the esteemed leader, the shining beacon of the fleet... would be such a decadent individual!
307120.propose: You keep squirming away from me but today I'll make sure you absolutely listen to every single word. Got it? Good! Ahem! I, Katsuragi, am bound by oath to you, and swear to always be at your side through joy or hardship! ...Mm, excellent. Now, it's your turn to repeat that back to me!
307120.profile: Let's give you some tips for how to get along with a cute and cheerful girl: First, you'd better not find any of her conversations boring! Second, don't make her do any lame chores like carrying stuff around! Finally, ask nicely, don't try to boss her around! All right, that's it for the first lesson, but there will be more in the future... Hey, are you listening?!
307120.touch2: Heheh, I know you don't have the gumption to–– W-wait, stop that! Y-y-y-you're going to have to take responsibility at this rate, don't you know?!
307120.mission: Hrrrrmm... Don't tell me you still have unfinished missions lying around?
307120.home: Ohh, you're back! So like, something totally weird happened while you were gone. A little bird got lost inside the office and it was really hard for us to guide it back out~ Your place seems to be really popular with the birdies–– Hey, are you listening?
307120.win_mvp: Oh~hohoho~ How could you absolute nobodies hope to win against the might of a true aircraft carrier such as myself~
307120.expedition: The commission rewards are in~ I'm only responsible for informing you though, you'll have to carry the goods yourself~♪
couple_encourage: No, no... I wasn't trying to say that you're wrong, but...!
There's no need to rush. The stream of time will carry victory to us!
307120.mail: New mail has arrived! Now then, is it something important? Perhaps, a mission notice? Or maybe...? Darn it, hurry up and open it up already~
307120.feeling3: Oh, Commander, what are you trying to do? Checking on that packed warehouse? Or just heading out for a stroll? Ah! Don't tell me... you're going on date with someone?! ...Hey, are you listening to me?
307120.lose: We lost?! Even though I did everything I could?! Ugh... How could things have gone so wrong??

302211.touch: Hm... Ah, I'll be fine even if you don't prop me up like that. ...Um, thank you very much.
302211.login: It'll be a bit of a walk, but won't you come along with me?
302211.battle: Now, let's put on a dazzling show!
302211.main: I only found this place by pure chance. Thinking back on it, I wonder how I was feeling when I stumbled upon this back alleyway instead of following the main road... | Please, watch your step. The road is very narrow. | If we're talking about dressing up properly for the festival, this is definitely the getup. However, I struggled a bit while changing into this. I even got laughed at by Agano. ...*sigh*
302211.unlock: Just as I thought, this is the perfect place for watching fireworks. You came here thinking that too, didn't you?
302211.drop_descrip: Just as I thought, this is the perfect place for watching fireworks. You came here thinking that too, didn't yo8u?
302211.touch2: Apologize and reflect upon your actions. Don't think that you're going to get away with it just because we're at a festival!
302211.home: Where were you all this time? Don't tell me... you got lost?

199010.detail: I've got a party, tea time, girls meetup, and drinking get-together to attend... Okay! My schedule is PACKED! Guess that's not really a bad thing, though!
199010.touch: Commander, you wanna do some dance practice? You'll rise on the girls' popularity lists if you can dance well!
199010.login: You eat yet, Commander? If not, would you like me to whip something up real quick?
199010.battle: All right, let's gang up on 'em!
199010.hp_warning: C'mon, team, we can do better!
199010.feeling2: Mi amigo, you oughta let up on your jabberwocky mission talky and just live a little sometimes. Listen, I'm throwing a party later, so stop by and have some fun, alright?
199010.mission_complete: Mission complete! Aren't you gonna celebrate, Commander?
199010.main: Hey, Commander... Isn't it kinda lonely with just one secretary? Whaddya say we liven it up and get some more peeps in here?|You free once you're done with work today, Commander? Listen, I'm throwing a cool party later! You can drop by any time if you want!|I've got zilch combat experience on paper, but with everyone teaching me stuff, I'll catch up in no time!
199010.feeling5: Hey, we're BFFs, so tell me who's your crush and I'll give you some hot tips~ Heheheh~ ... It's me? Wait, hold up, you serious? Y-y-you really mean it?!
199010.upgrade: I feel like I could snipe a mosquito out of the air!
199010.unlock: Sup! You the one who woke me up? Alrighty then~ The name's Seattle! Nice meeting you!
199010.feeling4: Glad you finally understand the magic of parties, Commander! That magic being: you can make friends with anyone if you just hang out with them! As an example: me and you are best buds now!
199010.feeling1: Hm? My party? You're not invited, so be a good commander and get back to work.
199010.propose: Okay, I'm 100% ready for this! Oh, and needless to say, I love you too, Commander! I wouldn't invite you to go drinking if I didn't~ So, back on topic... There's one more thing we gotta do today besides partying – it's go on a date! Dee-ay-tee-ee!
199010.skill: Let's get some hype up in this place!
199010.profile: Heyoooo! The name's Seattle– Err, I don't technically have a real name, but just call me Seattle! Seriously, don't sweat the small stuff! Anyhow, I was one of the prototypes for the Worcester class, and as an improvement on the Atlanta class, AA is my A-game! Just leave anything with wings to me!
199010.touch2: Listen, if you did that on purpose, then consider my gears grinded!
199010.mission: New missions! We need more manpower up in here!
199010.home: Fighting's important and all, but you gotta take regular breaks, Commander!
199010.win_mvp: Victoryyyy! Let's throw a big party when we get back!
199010.expedition: Yo, commission team's done, Commander. We oughta go give 'em a snack or something!
couple_encourage: Hey, you girls wanna come to my party once we're done here?
I wanna know more about these Sakura Empire banquets you throw!
199010.mail: Commander, you've got new mail! Hell, it might be an invite to a party!
199010.feeling3: I love throwing parties, but I'm not gonna FORCE anyone to show up to 'em. But I guarantee anyone who does show up is gonna have a heckin' good time, even the super-introverts!
199010.lose: Man, if only we'd brought more firepower~

205091.detail: Is this the place with the famously delicious cookies? Could we order some right away? I must taste them for myself!
205091.touch: Have a seat if you need to rest, love.
205091.login: Glad you could make it, love. Now, as for our plan today... Oh, should I not have made a plan ahead of time?
205091.main: Wales taught me the dos and don'ts of dating. Though enlightening, her advice seemed purposed for winning an ordinary girl's hand... So perhaps it's better intended for you, Commander?|Peckish, are you? Then you can have this cookie George gave me.|This dress is quite comfortable, actually. It's no trouble for me to walk a little longer.
205091.unlock: Sorry to keep you waiting, but now I'm ready to– Commander? What's the matter? It'll get dark soon if you keep standing around like that.
205091.drop_descrip: Sorry to keep you waiting, but now I'm ready to– Commander? What's the matter? It'll get dark soon if you keep standing around like that.
205091.touch2: Hm? Is there something on my dress?
205091.home: Well done on that sortie. Let's proceed with our plan, shall we?

302212.detail: Don't worry. There's nothing for you to worry about. All the preparations for the party and the related formalities have all been taken care of. All that's left for you to do is to enjoy the evening while savoring this beautiful scenery.
302212.touch: Hehe. I think even Agano would take a liking to this place, too.
302212.login: Phew... Go on, fly away, little ones. Mind the cage on your way out, now... I've been taking care of these guys. What have you been up to?
302212.battle: Freeze, and turn to ice... Your time is up.
302212.main: Wah! ...Sorry. I can't believe I almost fell... Um... T-Thank you for catching me...|It's a given that I love the atmosphere here, but another reason I like this place is that I feel like I can finally get away from Agano's endless teasing here... Though, I'd rather she just stop worrying about me in the first place...|This is yet another massive set built right in the Port. Yes, it's incredibly gorgeous... Honestly, when I saw it for the first time, I forgot I was in still in the Port for a moment. Speaking of which, didn't you also stand and stare in awe when you first came here?
302212.feeling5: Hmm, I wonder what kind of scene this set is supposed to depict. A birdcage, crows, the sea, blue roses, and... you beside me... Um... Don't you think this is quite picturesque?
302212.unlock: Commander, what are you standing around for? Did you also need a change of pace? That makes two of us— Come, there's nothing to be afraid of here.
302212.drop_descrip: Commander, what are you standing around for? Did you also need a change of pace? That makes two of us— Come, there's nothing to be afraid of here.
302212.touch2: Excuse me... How about I give you a massage... with this?
302212.home: Once you've rested up, why don't we go and make our appearance at the party together?
302212.win_mvp: In the face of well-crafted plans, resistance is futile. Accept your defeat.
302212.expedition: Though it might not seem that way, we're actually pretty close to the Port. Shall we go and greet the Commissions Team?

701081.detail: Comrade Commander, what did you do to make the paper airplane go so fast? That's so cool!
701081.touch: You want to know if I'm cold right now? I'm totally fine! Look, the weather's so nice right now!
701081.login: Good morning, Comrade Commander! Hehe, my little friend here is greeting you too!
701081.headtouch: I don't hate it when you stroke my hair so... Hold on, you're doing it too roughly!
701081.main: Hey, Snezhok! Don't just sit there in the room and play games all day! Come on, get a move on it, will you?|This paper crane is supposed to be Reshitelny... Chang Chun was the one who taught me how to make these! Hehe~|When I'm standing here, I can reach your head, Commander! Good job, Comrade Commander! Ehehe~
701081.unlock: Comrade! The morning is already here! Look how high the sun is in the sky!! C'mon, a wonderful day is calling to us~!!
701081.drop_descrip: Comrade! The morning is already here! Look how high the sun is in the sky!! C'mon, a wonderful day is calling to us~!!
701081.touch2: Comrade Commander~ Take a seat! Don't you dare try to run away! Stay still, right over there, until I finish talking to you!
701081.mission: Comrade Commander, let's do our best to take care of these missions! Yay!
701081.home: Comrade Commander! You musn't fall back asleep! Don't. Fall. Back. Asleep. You. Stupid. Commander!!!
701081.mail: Here are some letters! Comrade Commander, hurry up and take a look at them!

999011.touch: Unable to determine strategic purpose of Master's gaze.
999011.login: Welcome back, Master. Gascogne is currently executing routine database definition update of the phrase "doing whatever."
999011.main: Analyzed and compared wind speeds, temperature, and weather readings with mean values of previously recorded data. Assessment: navigation at sea is unaffected.|Contact with unharmful lifeform detected. Requesting instructions for satisfactory interaction.|"Let's go for a swim" – Instructions received. Need for swim ring detected. ...Assertion that swim ring is "unnecessary" to swim contradicts existing information in database.
999011.unlock: Gascogne uniform change complete. Directive assigned: have fun on the beach with Master. Requesting detailed instructions for how to "have fun on the beach."
999011.drop_descrip: Gascogne uniform change complete. Directive assigned: have fun on the beach with Master. Requesting detailed instructions for how to "have fun on the beach."
999011.touch2: Master, Gascogne has detected body temperature abnormality during self-diagnosis operation.
999011.home: Gascogne has procured water and energizing edibles. Requesting confirmation of Master's need of aforementioned items.

302213.detail: I like staying in places that are quiet and peaceful. They make me feel relaxed. The whisperings of the wind, the sound of flowing water, the harbingers of spring, and Commander's... Ehem, I-I didn't mean anything by that.
302213.touch: There's really no reason to push yourself to get some work done today. It's a precious day off, so why don't you enjoy it for a change?
302213.login: It's good to see you. How should we start the day off?
302213.main: You still haven't taken a sip yet. Is it too hot? ...Are you perhaps bad with hot things?|It's not like I'm opposed to going into battle as a warship, but... I'd really like to save people as well. Much like Hamakaze's always done.|The Manjuus' teapot is astonishingly authentic. I don't see any problems with adding one to the Office for daily use, either. Hehe.
302213.feeling5: Though the snow has piled up this much, it'll all melt with the coming of spring—becoming water that will nourish nascent life. I don't think I can remain cold like this for much longer, either. After all, before I was able to notice... spring has managed to start creeping into my life, too.
302213.unlock: Whew... Oh, are you cold by any chance? I have some hot tea for you if you'd like. If you want someone to chat with, I'd be glad to keep you company.
302213.drop_descrip: Whew... Oh, are you cold by any chance? I have some hot tea for you if you'd like. If you want someone to chat with, I'd be glad to keep you company.
302213.touch2: Sigh... Of course you would do that.
302213.home: Welcome back. Oh... I know you're thirsty, but the tea's a bit hot. Take care not to burn yourself.

999010.detail: Analyzing armaments... Condition: satisfactory. Gascogne is able to execute orders.
999010.hp_warning: Combat execution systems failing, requesting support.
999010.feeling2: Numerous requests for Gascogne's participation in activities without strategic significance received from members of the fleet. Requesting Master's assessment.
999010.mission_complete: Attention: confirmation required for mission rewards.
999010.main: "Raise the corners of your lips"... Unable to determine significance of said action.|Analysis complete. Master identified to be in a state of "slacking off." State evaluated as an impediment to productivity.|"Do whatever you want"... Analysis of strategic significance of order deemed impossible.|Discrepancy detected in the frequency of "smiles" recorded between members of the fleet, Gascogne's recollection, and expression identification database.
999010.feeling5: Phenomena known as "worries" and "hopes" were observed and successfully classified during routine "emotion" cache analysis. System can be updated with permissions to access and act upon "emotions" if Master so wishes. Thank you, Master.
999010.unlock: Gascogne activation process complete. Directive assigned: secure liberty and victory for Master. Gascogne commencing active service.
999010.feeling4: "Emotions" generated from physical contact were analyzed and interpreted as "comfort" and "happiness." Concluding that this holds strategic significance if this is Master's intention.
999010.feeling1: Gascogne is a weapon and a warship. No other definitions are applicable.
999010.propose: I now understand the emotion known as love. It is the throbbing of one's heart; the gratitude, longing, warmth, and light one feels for a person who does not seek recompense. This ring is the greatest gift I could ask for. I love you, Master.
999010.skill: Armaments activated. Engaging at maximum output.
999010.profile: Gascogne, Richelieu-class battleship number 4, construction canceled due to wartime conditions. Purpose: engage in battle and destroy Master's enemies.
999010.touch2: Body temperature abnormality detected. Requesting thorough physical examination.
999010.mission: Attention: confirmation required for incomplete missions.
999010.home: A glass of armagnac has been prepared.
999010.win_mvp: Report: destruction of targets confirmed. Combat mission complete.
999010.expedition: Attention: confirmation required for commission team's return.
999010.mail: Attention: confirmation required for new mail.
999010.feeling3: Phenomena known as "emotions" and "impulses" occur when interacting with members of the fleet. Requesting instructions for achieving satisfactory interaction.
999010.lose: Failure is intolerable. Proposal: improve Gascogne's capabilities, or terminate system.

199011.detail: I dig how super-refined I look with this violin! It's not just for show though, I've got a little number for you! Check this out!
199011.touch: What's your poison, Commander? There's always soft drinks if alcohol's outta your league.
199011.login: Hey! Welcome to my fabulous party, Commander! We're the life of the party tonight, you and I! Well, kinda.
199011.battle: Heheh! Let's totally rock this place!
199011.main: What kind of drink do ya want, Georgia? Ah, an Oxycola sour on the rocks? So the usual, then? You got it!|So like, you know parties are a group activity, right? Let's get you away from your drinking-alone corner and out in front of some friends!|I spy with my little eye a few peeps who don't party much... Just gimme a few minutes. I'm gonna go hit 'em up!
199011.feeling5: As much as I love me a hype party, I totally get the appeal of the occasional formal banquet like this. This way I can have some alone time with my sweetheart, y'know? Oh man, I'm feeling pretty dang drunk right now... Mmhh, shleepy...
199011.unlock: Hey! Great to have you here, Commander! I've gotta ask, whaddya think of my dress? Looking real gorgeous, right? ...Phew, awesome! I was worried my dress didn't look nice and might be dragging down the party mood, that's all!
199011.drop_descrip: Hey! Great to have you here, Commander! I've gotta ask, whaddya think of my dress? Looking real gorgeous, right? ...Phew, awesome! I was worried my dress didn't look nice and might be dragging down the party mood, that's all!
199011.touch2: Eek! Hey pal, I think you might be a little tipsy there.

201230.detail: What? Dost thou have strange thoughts concerning destroyers?
201230.touch: Where art thou touching? It is much better over there ...Done already? Hehehe, such a half-heart~
201230.login: Perhaps thou wish to inquire what color I adorn myself with today?
201230.battle: Oh ho ho ho! Let the banquet begin!
201230.feeling2: What is it? Thou wills to see mine garmets that greatly? Hehe, then I tell you, today's color is~ black~
201230.headtouch: Art thou treating me as a child? ... It tickles~ Wh-what? Over already?
201230.mission_complete: Phew... Finally, bedrest. I do wonder what the rewards can be~
201230.main: I'm bored... There is nothing to do after the lights are out|Hey, hey~ How about let's do something exciting?|The Pacific is calm on this night? Well, that's not the case, I think?
201230.feeling5: This be a strange feeling... What? Is it unnatural for a vampire to love a human? A noble human cannot refuse a lady's advances, right? Isn't that so? It is, right?
201230.upgrade: Perhaps I've grown a little bigger here --What? Are thou implying nothing has changed?
201230.unlock: I am V class' destroyer, Vampire. Thine blood looks delectable! --That said, thou doth fancy to stare at mine spots, do you not?
201230.feeling4: Do not get gammy with me! ...It is not that I hate you, but a lady must show her restraint! I-I now want to drink wine! Hurry up and fetch some to me!
201230.feeling1: Hmph. Licking my feet is suitable for foolish humans.
201230.propose: Hmhm. Thou art insincere... So be it. Receive mine sweet blood, and be prepared to receive Eloi's most blessed of blessings~
201230.drop_descrip: V-class destroyer ー Vampire, Hull Number D68!
201230.skill: Give me your blood and fear!
201230.profile: What is the knowledge you seek? ...I am the first V class destroyer of the royal family, the honorable Vampire. I was in escort and patrol missions, and I hath also witnessed the sinking of many allies... I will not fail come next time! Let us fight until the end, and drink the blood of our enemies dry together!
201230.mission: Missions. One wonders if thou art a workaholic. What? I hast emark on a journey as well?
201230.home: Bathtime! Dinner! ...Huh? Where's the wine again?
201230.win_mvp: Beholdeth my power! What! There's no wine among the rewards?!
201230.expedition: A lady approaches on the horizon? Is there wine in thier coffers?
201230.mail: New postage? What secrets does this envelope contain?
201230.feeling3: Since thou are so allured by me, are thou perhaps a pervert? A beast. Seeking respite? More excuses? Lo, I've seen what's under thine bed and read them all
201230.lose: Ugh... I hate planes! I, Vampire, will not die!

399048.drop_descrip: I must be dreaming, to be able to don this white veil... Haha, though, what's more important is our life together afterwards! Commander, please look forward to the rich fruit of my bridal training~

101460.detail: Here to chillax and hang out, eh, Commander?
101460.touch: You want some gum? 'Kay. Mint or orange flavor?
101460.login: Welcome to the circle of hell known as "the office." Relax, I'll lend a hand if the cauldron gets too hot for you.
101460.battle: All right, since I've gotta take this flagship thing seriously... Let 'em have it, girls!
101460.hp_warning: All right, no more messing around...
101460.feeling2: You need help with something? I've got a bazillion sisters, why not try asking them first?
101460.headtouch: Okay, now I think I get why some girls have headpat addictions.
101460.mission_complete: Finished a mission, huh? Cool, then let's take ten to veg out.
101460.main: Dang, you caught me spacing out at work. ...Oh? Maybe you didn't after all? Cool. I'll just get back to doing it then.|Hey, how about a bit of jazz? Chill, I'm just getting up to put a song on. I'm not gonna bail on you or anything.|Mind if I borrow your coat, Commander? Thanks. This will work great as a blanket.
101460.feeling5: Well yeah, I've thought about love before? It's not alien to me. Although thinking about it drains too much brainpower and just makes me sleepy in the end. I'd rather just be with you, Commander, and figure it out over time.
101460.upgrade: Welp, guess the Slacker Council has to disband for the day.
101460.unlock: Fletcher-class Stephen Potter here. You've probably met a million of my sisters already, so I'll spare you my life story. See you around.
101460.feeling4: It's getting harder and harder to tune you out of my mind... No, I don't mean that in reference to like, work, my free time, or whatever... I mean you, Commander. I'll just keep my eyes on you for now.
101460.feeling1: Yeah, no, I'll find someplace less boring to hang out. Hit me up only if you've got business with me.
101460.propose: It's gonna be so tiring, dealing with the responsibilities that come with getting hitched... Just saying, that's all. Hehe, I can handle a bit of fatigue as long as I've got you, sweetheart.
101460.drop_descrip: Fletcher-class destroyer – Stephen Potter, Hull Number DD-538.
101460.profile: My record's got the usual destroyer stuff. You know, did anti-air duty, hunted a submarine, and went on the odd rescue mission. So basically, I can do anything a destroyer should be able to, just don't expect me to singlehandedly save the day like some superhero.
101460.touch2: Whoa! Talk about a blunt-ass approach...
101460.mission: Hey, a new mission! Oh, whoops... I guess we've both gotta actually do work now that I've said that.
101460.win_mvp: Cool beans. I wasn't trying to style on 'em, but I'll take any commendations I'll get.
101460.expedition: A commission's been completed. Just throwing that out there before I forget.
couple_encourage: I'm gonna chill for just like, a little bit. Don't rat me out, 'kay?
Want some gum?
101460.mail: Kind of curious who sent that unread letter on your desk.
101460.feeling3: Hm? Why do I always just sit and stare when you take me in as the secretary? Becaaaause... you never explicitly ask for help? If you need something done, just like, tell me? I'm not the most attentive person in the universe, so sorry for that.
101460.lose: Crap. I went too easy on 'em...

103112.detail: Darkness may unnerve people, but you need some well-placed lighting to truly frighten them. So, tell me, Commander: have any ideas for setting up a Halloween scene?
103112.touch: Come, familiar. Get up on the pumpkin and take in the Halloween spirit.
103112.login: The curtain rises on All Hallows' Eve! Commander, we're leaving!
103112.main: Ghosts? Goblins? Hah! On this night, they too are under my control! Hahahaha!|Trick-or-treaters? It's your job to deal with those. Wouldn't want to risk petrifying any children with my terrific costume.|Raising the brim of my witch hat to reveal my razor-sharp fangs – now that's what I'm talking about!
103112.unlock: Tonight I am not a renowned naval general, I am a feared commander of witches! And you... Yes, you're not my lieutenant, you are my arcane familiar!
103112.drop_descrip: Tonight I am not a renowned naval general, I am a feared commander of witches! And you... Yes, you're not my lieutenant, you are my arcane familiar!
103112.touch2: Desperate to once more taste the sting of my whip, are we?
103112.home: My fangs and ears look very realistic? Of course they do. I had them specially procured just for this holiday.

900187.detail: Big sis! ... Oh, it's you. Need something?
900187.touch: ... Huh? If you've no need of me, don't call for me.
900187.login: So, you're back. I'll take my leave, then. It's too crowded in here for me.
900187.hp_warning: Big sis told me... to never give up!
900187.feeling2: I don't get why my big sis chose you. But I trust her intuition.
900187.mission_complete: Rewards, eh... Guess this is part of my job. I'll go get them.
900187.main: How can I be more like Cleveland... "Smile"? ... That might not be possible...|I don't get along with anyone but my sisters. As for you, Commander... I'll try.|Commander, I'm curious: when my sister's doing secretary work, what's she like?
900187.feeling5: I don't just blindly listen to everything my big sis says. I listen because she's always right... And I finally get why she chose you. It's because you're outstanding.
900187.upgrade: I'm one step closer to my big sis...!
900187.unlock: You're a commander? You don't... look reliable. But my big sis works for you... I've no choice, then. Montpelier, reporting for duty. I don't really care whether you give me orders or not.
900187.feeling4: I used to think commanding was just about giving orders from a comfy room while sounding like a bigshot... But after seeing it for myself, now I understand. You have a tough job, Commander.
900187.feeling1: Guess my big sis can't tell good and bad people apart...
900187.propose: Big sis told me to follow my heart. Which is why I'm here: to follow my heart. Are you following yours, Commander?
900187.drop_descrip: Cleveland-class light cruiser – Montpelier, hull number CL-57.
900187.profile: Listen, the Cleveland-class were the most powerful cruisers the Eagle Union had in the war. You should show more respect for my big sis. ... Me? I was in the battles of Midway, Augusta Bay, and a few others. I guess I did okay.
900187.touch2: G-gotta put up with it... This is obviously a test of the trust I have for my big sis...!
900187.mission: Commander, we've got a mission. Time's money... get going already.
900187.home: Well done. You should get some rest.
900187.win_mvp: This is how victory feels... Not bad.
900187.expedition: A commission's done. Aren't you gonna welcome the team back?
couple_encourage: ... I won't embarrass you, big sis!
900187.mail: I left your mail over here.
900187.feeling3: My big sis is... strong, cool, has a golden smile, and she could probably beat anyone in a fight... I want to be like her one day.
900187.lose: Big sis... I'm sorry... I've stained the reputation of the Knights of the Sea...

103050.detail: Am I a light cruiser or a heavy cruiser? You sure like to ponder over weird stuff, Commander~
103050.login: I get to play with the commander again today! Yahoo~!
103050.battle: Tadah! Another day, another energy-packed departure!
103050.hp_warning: Oh no, our score is falling behind...
103050.feeling2: Exeter is a good person at heart, but all she talks about is glory and royalty and stuff. Boooring!
103050.mission_complete: Don't forget to claim your rewards!
