103050.feeling5: Commander, how about we just relax today instead of going out to play? I... I have something I want to tell you, so listen up, okay?
103050.upgrade: Whoosh! Houston's breaking through the first escape velocity!
103050.unlock: Hiya! I'm Houston, fifth ship of the Northampton-class. I single-handedly took on Sakura Empire reinforcements in the Battle of the Sunda Strait! I hope I'll get to play with you every day from now on! Yahoo~!
103050.feeling4: Houston, you've got a problem... Commander, whenever I see you, I get so anxious I can't even speak properly... What should I do...
103050.feeling1: You're no fun at all, Commander...
103050.propose: Thank you, Commander~ I love you~! Hehe, you don't need to be so serious about! Come on, let's go somewhere and play!
103050.drop_descrip: Northampton-class Heavy Cruiser – Houston, Hull Number CA-30!
103050.profile: Hiya! I'm Houston, fifth ship of the Northampton-class! I received a Medal of Honor from the President for facing off against an entire Sakura Empire squadron in the Battle of the Java Sea and the Battle of Sunda Strait, all on my own! I'm really proud of it~!
103050.touch2: Gosh, Commander... you're a real weirdo... aren't you!
103050.mission: Co~man~der~! You've still got some unfinished missions!
103050.home: Hehe~ Fighting's what a soldier does, right!
103050.expedition: Mister rocket and mister plane are friends yet again~... Hm? Commander, a commission's been completed!
couple_encourage: This feels strangely familiar...
Turkey Squad, attack! Wait, that's not right!
103050.mail: Commander, Commander! There's mail for you!
103050.feeling3: Bang! Ratatatata! ... Whew, today's been a lot of fun! I really love playing with you, Commander~
103050.lose: Ooow... My head's spinning... I think I bumped into something even harder than me...

900186.detail: You wanna get to know me? Sure thing. Inspect me to your heart's content.
900186.touch: Gee, thanks! You made my bubble pop!
900186.login: Another day of calm weather! Nice!
900186.battle: Dang, guess I've got no choice! I'll show you the might of us Southerners!
900186.feeling2: Commander, it's sunny outside, so why don't we go for a walk? It's unhealthy to stay indoors all the time!
900186.mission_complete: Today's missions were a breeze! Total walk in the park!
900186.main: What tunes do I listen to? Good question. See if you can guess! ... Rock 'n' roll? Bzzzt, wrong!|Bleh, my sis snatched my sunglasses again...|Once this war is over, maybe I should give Eagle Union football a try...
900186.feeling5: When I can't see you on my days off, I feel kinda lonely... Geez, look at you, making a girl say stuff like this! A-aren't you ashamed of yourself?! Jerk!
900186.unlock: Cleveland-class light cruiser number 2, Columbia! That's me~! Not the Columbia in D.C., the one in South Carolina! Geez, listen to me! Not the Columbia with Bogotá as its capital!
900186.feeling4: Why do I wear only one sock? That's a secret! If you're so curious, try taking it off~ Hehehe♪
900186.feeling1: *Sigh*... So that's all, huh. I was wrong to get my hopes up.
900186.propose: Yeah... thanks. Even when we're not on the battlefield, we'll always be together... No, wait, cheesy lines like this are totally out of character for me! Anyhow, right now, I feel so happy!
900186.drop_descrip: Cleveland-class light cruiser – Columbia, hull number CL-56.
900186.skill: Don't blame me if you get hit!
900186.profile: Hiii! It's me, the girl who scooted through the Pacific and earned 10 battle stars: Columbia! Hey, now, no need to sing my praises, go see Cleveland and sing hers instead! Need anything else? Alright, then I'll get back to patrolling.
900186.touch2: Commander, is it this star on my shirt you like? Or is it... what's underneath it~?
900186.mission: I only just started chewing this gum, and we've already got a new mission...?
900186.home: You're back~! I've been chewing on this gum so long it's lost all its taste.
900186.win_mvp: That was nothing special~ I do it all the time~
900186.expedition: The commission team's back! Aren't you gonna go thank them?
couple_encourage: Hey, sis~ You really do need my support, don't you?
900186.mail: Aren't you gonna check your mail? There might be something nice in there.
900186.feeling3: Hm? You'd never have guessed that I'd be into ballet? ... What's that supposed to mean?! Laugh one more time and I'll punch you!

199012.detail: I've gotta show everyone who walks through these doors how passionate the Eagle Union is about our Christmas celebrations!
199012.touch: Pass the salt shaker this way! Thanks!
199012.login: Yooo! Awesome! With your help, Commander, we're gonna speed through things twice as fast... no, three times!
199012.main: Georgia, the gingerbread you wanted is ready! There's a little surprise waiting for you! |Hmm, let me think, what are we still missing...? Ah! A special Christmas tree that can immediately grab everyone's attention! |The holidays give us all a reason to get together and have a good time. As for me, I'm in charge of providing the best venue for that to happen!
199012.unlock: Meeeerry Christmas~! Even though the party is about to start, as you can see, I'm still getting ready~ Just gimme a moment, all righty~?
199012.drop_descrip: Meeeerry Christmas~! Even though the party is about to start, as you can see, I'm still getting ready~ Just gimme a moment, all righty~?
199012.touch2: Commander, now's not the time for that!
199012.home: All righty, that should about do it for the food preparations.

601020.detail: Commander, I'm currently on patrol. Do you have any new instructions for me?
601020.hp_warning: This isn't how it was supposed to be...
601020.feeling2: Rest assured, Commander. This subordinate shall always be loyal to you.
601020.mission_complete: The missions are done, and we have quite the rewards to show for it. If there were some non-material rewards though...
601020.main: Royal submarines have always been elusive and mercurial. They've gotten the better of me in the past... |My gun? I'm telling you, it's real! I just don't have it loaded. |"Don't disturb during work hours." I put this sign up so you can have your peace of mind!
601020.feeling5: Commander, are you heading out? Do you need a bodyguard... Oh, it's just a civilian errand? N-no! Even if it's just across the street, y-you never know what hazards lie in wait... S-so, let's go together!
601020.upgrade: I shall definitely become a better subordinate!
601020.unlock: Flagship Veneto's escort, Carabiniere of the Sardegna Empire, reporting for duty! As your subordinate, I will carry out your orders and complete any mission!
601020.feeling4: Commander, I'm really flattered that you treat me so well... You feel safe when I'm by your side? Understood. Your subordinate shall work harder in that regard!
601020.feeling1: Commander, I don't think that... Nevermind, your subordinate shall follow your order.
601020.propose: From now on, this subordinate shall serve you for life! ...That's not what it means? Um, then... I see! B-but, can someone like me really be your partner?
601020.profile: As a member of the Soldati-class destroyers, I served as the leader of the 12th Destroyer Squadron and led my compatriots through many battles. No matter when or where, I shall give it my all to complete any mission!
601020.touch2: P-please don't tease your subordinates like that!
601020.mission: Commander, there are still tasks that need to be finished. Do you require anything of me?
601020.home: Commander, an inquiry arrived while you were gone. Do you want to look it over?
601020.expedition: The commission team has returned! I'm so glad that everyone came back safely.
601020.mail: Commander, the mailbox seems to be filling up.
601020.feeling3: Commander, if you plan on going out, please let me be your bodyguard!
601020.lose: Ugh... th-this subordinate will accept any punishment!

201231.detail: Commander, where art thee looking? ...! I-it's only because the dress is tight-fitting!
201231.touch: Commander, dost thee enjoy touching me? "My skin is smooth and fair?" Ehehe, I love thy sweet-talking~
201231.main: Dost thee have plans for tonight? Ehehe, I do~ I plan to cling to thee all night so thee cannot go anywhere~ |My favourite meal? Ehehe, obviously the one after I have blown out the candles~ |I wish to do fun things~ with the person I like~
201231.unlock: What dost thee think of my new dress? Like it? Or love it~? Eheh~ 'tis written all over thy face. Next is... w-wait! I haven't put on my stockings yet!
201231.drop_descrip: What dost thee think of my new dress? Like it? Or love it~? Eheh~ 'tis written all over thy face. Next is... w-wait! I haven't put on my stockings yet!
201231.touch2: Ehehe, Commander is a pervert who only I could love~

900188.login: Hey, Commander! You seem to be in a good mood today!
900188.battle: I'm in a hurry... just come at me all at once, alright?
900188.feeling2: What is, Commander? Something troubling you? I've got lots of little sisters, so I'm used to giving them my shoulder to lean on. So if anything's got you down, just tell me.
900188.mission_complete: Nice! We got some mission rewards!
900188.main: Never regret the choices you make!|Why do you call me "Clevebro"?! I'm a girl, just like the others!|You know, I like trees. Let's grow a bonsai, Commander!
900188.feeling5: I feel like I've told you everything about myself... Time sure flies, doesn't it... I doubt someone who understands me the way you do will ever show up again. That's why I've...
900188.unlock: Pleasure meeting you, Commander! I'm Cleveland, a knight of the sea! Come on, time is money! We can't afford to take a break!
900188.feeling4: Before I realized it, I'm the one who's leaning on your shoulder instead... but hey, that's fine. We can always just rely on each other.
900188.feeling1: Sorry, my sisters are waiting for me. I don't have time to deal with you.
900188.propose: Heh, I had a feeling this would happen! From now on, you can tell me anything. I'll take excellent care of you!
900188.drop_descrip: Cleveland-class Light Cruiser – Cleveland, Hull Number CL-55!
900188.profile: I'm the big sister of the Cleveland-class... but I guess that's obvious from my name alone. I fought through the Battle of Renelle Island, the Battle of Empress Augusta Bay, plus many others, and I earned around 13 battle stars, so I'm pretty strong!
900188.touch2: You can't do this sorta stuff in public, Commander...
900188.mission: We've got a new mission! Let's finish it in one go!
900188.home: Ah, Commander, let me give you a massage... Just bear with me!
900188.win_mvp: Hehe, now this is what I'd call the fruits of my hard labor!
900188.expedition: Hehe, it's about time we reap the rewards of that commission, Commander!
couple_encourage: Come on, fellow big sisters. Let's work hard together!
"Hao" do you do, folks?
900188.mail: Some new mail just arrived. You sure are popular, Commander!
900188.feeling3: Mm... I'm not trying to make myself look stronger than I am or anything, but honestly, I think there aren't many people like you who I can speak to like an equal...

100010.detail: Staring at me all day won't turn you into an expert!
100010.login: Righty tighty, Lefty loosey, Stay calm and Purin on!
100010.battle: Purin~! Don't stop until they kneel and cry!
100010.feeling2: My sister is so dumb. When people talk about our colors, it's not about our hair, it's about ra... rari... ah, now I remember! Reality TV!
100010.mission_complete: I'm just heading out to fetch your rewards, purin! I promise I won't break them!
100010.main: Purin~! It's so big in here! There's so much room to run around!|Oh right, it's not my job to just run around, is it? Purin~!|Purin~? I'm too loud? Hmph, who cares what you think!
100010.feeling5: You're not an average commander if you managed to conquer my heart. But I won't be shy or blush! Instead I'll give you a growl! Graaaah!
100010.unlock: Purin~! The herald of good fortune has arrived! Are you ready? Raise your hands and follow me... Purin~ purin~!
100010.feeling4: Whee~! I'm flying! So~ high! Hey, don't move! You'll have to catch me if I fall!
100010.feeling1: You're pretty amazing to have gotten on my bad side! But I won't get angry just to appease you! Haha! Enjoy your emptiness!
100010.propose: As a simple Bulin, I'm meant to just help strengthen your other ships... But you gave me this ring... You're a strange one! I like you! Come, let's raise our hands together and say purin~ purin~!
100010.drop_descrip: Prototype Bulin MKII. Can be used to limit break all Super Rare ships.
100010.skill: My drill is the drill that will pierce the heavens!
100010.profile: Hahaha! It's your lucky day now that you've met me! We can purin together from this day forward! What for? To make everyone stronger, obviously! How do you purin? Like this! Purin~! Purin~!
100010.touch2: Purin~ purin~! (Prototype Bulin MKII continues to spin faster)
100010.mission: Purin~! The next mission has been chosen for you!
100010.home: Let's run around and relax! Purin~!
100010.expedition: Yaaaay~! Commander! The girls who went out on a commission have come back! Let's drill something to celebrate!
100010.feeling3: I'll let you in on a little secret. My little sister keeps telling people that she's smarter than me. But truth is, she's dumber! I try to be nice and let her feel good about herself, like a big sister should. Ha!
100010.lose: So why am I on the battlefield anyway, purin?!

900182.win_mvp: Heheh~ The goddess of victory now stands on our side!
900182.lose: Never again... will I repeat the failures of the past!

301410.touch: Commander, want some? I don't mind sharing.
301410.battle: That's the enemy... can we eat them?
301410.feeling2: Commander, want to eat some taiyaki with me?
301410.mission_complete: Commander, does the reward include any taiyaki?
301410.main: I'm full... and sleepy... Commander, gimme a hug~|I like taiyaki filled with bean paste even in their tail fins.|Taiyaki looks like a fish... Fish live in the sea! Hm... the sea is on Earth! Earth is in space! Mm... so tasty!
301410.feeling5: "Only really close people should help each other get dressed"? Are we not close, Commander? I love you, Commander. Do you not like me?
301410.upgrade: I ate... too much taiyaki... I'm stuffed...
301410.unlock: Aahh... Hm? Hmm? Co... main... der? I'm Mikazuki. Want some taiyaki? You can have half of mine.
301410.feeling4: Always telling me to wear my clothes... you're just like my mom... But I still like you, Commander. Almost as much as I like taiyaki... Okay, Commander, help me get dressed.
301410.feeling1: Ahh~ *Nom* (Mikazuki doesn't seem to notice you.)
301410.propose: A promise...? Does that mean you'll help me get dressed? I don't really get it... I should really do it on my own...? Commander, you're weird... I'm fine with you helping me get dressed, I told you before...
301410.skill: You're not getting any of my taiyaki!
301410.profile: I'm Mikazuki. I've got a lot of little and big sisters. We're all friends. I'm really good at escort and transport missions! Oh, and I love taiyaki! Do you want some too, Commander?
301410.home: Ah... Commander, want some too? I've got more.
301410.win_mvp: Isn't it about time for a snack?
301410.expedition: Commander, I'm heading out to welcome back the commission team! They promised they'd buy me some taiyaki!
301410.mail: Commander, what's this package for? Can I pack up my taiyaki?
301410.feeling3: Clothes are so annoying... I hate getting dressed... I just want to eat taiyaki...

301162.detail: Zzzz... Fwah! Did I doze off just now...?! ...It's probably because I had to stay up all night helping Mullany with her cooking... how the heck did such a simple recipe turn into that massive project?!
301162.touch: Ehh?! Y-You're going to give me New Year's money?!
301162.login: Heheh~ As long as the lucky Yukikaze is at your side, everything's going to be smooth sailing this year!
301162.main: Is it snowing?! Hooray! Now I can play in the... A-ahem! Commander, why don't we go enjoy the scenery together? |That Chang Chun girl gave me some special-looking firecrackers. They look pretty neat, so can we set them off right now? Ehh?! I can't...? |Happy New Year! In the Dragon Empery, it doesn't count as a new year 'til this time rolls around! Of course Yukikaze the Wise would know that~♪
301162.unlock: Wa ha ha~! Did your heart skip a beat from seeing the charming Yukikaze? Hmph... Well, looks like the Dragon Empery girls are setting off firecrackers... let's go join them! Here, make sure to hold on to my hand!
301162.drop_descrip: Wa ha ha~! Did your heart skip a beat from seeing the charming Yukikaze? Hmph... Well, looks like the Dragon Empery girls are setting off firecrackers... let's go join them! Here, make sure to hold on to my hand!
301162.mission: Hmm... Let's finish the work first, then play later.

213021.detail: "From the depths of Sheol, I emerge from eternal slumber to claim your soul" ... This line sounds like something my sister would say.
213021.touch: Commander's hand... is nice and warm...
213021.login: Boo! Scaring people... it's done like this, right?
213021.main: I wanted to spend some time with my sister, but she doesn't seem to be interested in Halloween...|Today, everyone will be dressed up as monsters and witches, so I will fit in with them...|Children will ask for candy from adults... but Terror is no longer a child- Eh? Candy, for me? Thank you...
213021.unlock: I have to dress up as a ghost for Halloween, but I'm not very good at making complicated costumes... Is something like this okay?
213021.drop_descrip: I have to dress up as a ghost for Halloween, but I'm not very good at making complicated costumes... Is something like this okay?
213021.touch2: If you keep touching, the bandages are going to come lose...

102252.detail: My feelings for you haven't changed, but yeah, these clothes make me act really intimidating... Maybe I'm getting into my role too much.
102252.login: How's it going, Commander? It might be unprofessional of me to ask, but... Is something up?
102252.main: Let's take a ride to the party. Don't worry about the Manjuu, I've seen how well he can drive... What, that wasn't your concern?|You oughta take today off at the very least. No need to be a busy bee and work day in, day out.|Mental clarity is the key to keeping your cool on the battlefield. My sisters, they all have the fortitude it takes.
102252.feeling5: I came here intent on enjoying the party, but I wound up slipping into acting instead... Although, there's fun to be had in that, too. Listen, Commander, I'm sorry to ask, but I wanna know: are you... enjoying yourself?
102252.unlock: "Hehe... Now that you've finally fallen into my hands, why don't we take the day to get to know each other real well, Commander?" Oh my, was my acting a bit too realistic~?
102252.drop_descrip: "Hehe... Now that you've finally fallen into my hands, why don't we take the day to get to know each other real well, Commander?" Oh my, was my acting a bit too realistic~?
102252.touch2: "Looks like someone here doesn't know proper manners."
102252.win_mvp: "Clear out the rest of these fools, will you?" Hahah, guess there'll be no need for that.

102190.detail: My dream is to one day be as pretty as my sis, St. Louis!
102190.login: C-Commander... I haven't decided on how to do my hair yet, so please don't come barging in...
102190.hp_warning: Wh-what should I do, what should I do?!
102190.feeling2: Jeez, Commander, how many times have I told you not to just barge into a girl's room?! ... Huh?
102190.mission_complete: The mission rewards are here? Good job, Commander!
102190.main: Big sis is just like a model, always changing into all kinds of clothes... B-but, if everyone thinks her clothes are cute, it's probably not too bad... |Huh? Who's that blonde-haired boy always surrounded by everyone? Um, I... I'm not particularly interested or anything... |Commander, do I look cute today?
102190.feeling5: I wonder why... my heart always flutters when you help me do my hair... It's totally different from when big sis does it... Hopefully, I'm not sick or something...
102190.upgrade: Commander, I'll help rub your back~!
102190.unlock: How should I do my hair today~? Huh? Wh-who are you? Why are you in my room? Huh? This isn't my room...? Eh? Ehhhh...?!
102190.feeling4: Before, it was always big sis who helped me style my hair and put on makeup. But now, you're here to help me too! Ehehe, thank you, Commander~♪
102190.feeling1: Commander, it's no fun being with you... I-I'm leaving!
102190.propose: Big sis always told me that an "Oath" was the proof of a deep bond... In other words, Commander and I are going to always get along and be together forever, right? Ehehe, I'm so glad~!
102190.profile: I'm the Brooklyn-class light cruiser, Helena. I'm good at anti-air, and I like dressing up. Even though I seem to have come to a weird place, my big sis, St. Louis, taught me that a proper lady must remain calm at all times. You don't seem to be a shady person, so I guess I'll be your care.
102190.touch2: Commander, all the girls will hate you if you do stuff like this!
102190.mission: Commander, what do you think about the idea of wearing this hairstyle out to a mission?
102190.home: Commander, do you have time to help comb my hair?
102190.win_mvp: Heehee, I am the cutest after all~
102190.expedition: Commander, big sis told me before that nobody likes tardy people.
couple_encourage: H-hello! I'm H-Huh... Lena!
102190.mail: Huh... there's new mail? Commander, would you mind getting it yourself? I'm... having a bit of a bad hair day...
102190.feeling3: Commander, this hairstyle is really popular right now. Um, I still think I prefer this other one though better though... Which do you prefer?

601040.detail: If only Libeccio was here... I wouldn't have to agonize over how to talk to the commander...
601040.login: Greetings, greetings... G-good morning to you, Commander...
601040.battle: As the flagship... I've got to boost everyone's morale... Roar...!
601040.hp_warning: What should I do...? What should I do?!
601040.feeling2: Libeccio, please don't bother the commander in the middle of work hours... Here, I'll make a syllabus of the times when the commander is available. Mm, that should be right... hopefully.
601040.mission_complete: Mission complete. Umm, should I go help you confirm the rewards after all...?
601040.main: What do I think of Libeccio? ...She's my precious little sister. She can be a bit of a klutz at times though, ehehe...|The documents I was just working on are over here, and the already-finished ones are here... Ah, it's not that I couldn't find them, I just thought it'd be more efficient to remind myself out loud... S-sorry... *blushes*|Commander, you must be tired... Ahh, just thinking about it makes me nervous...
601040.feeling5: Um, Commander, please take this...! Libeccio told me that if there ever was something I'd never be able to say... to put it down in a picture book! P-please take a look...!
601040.upgrade: Shelling, torpedoes, and reloading... I must becoming stronger in all aspects...
601040.unlock: Now lift the rim of your skirt and bow... Ahem! I'm Maestrale, d-destroyer from the Sardegna Empire. Greetings to you and your fleet, Commander. I hope I did that right...
601040.feeling4: ...Commander? Why'd you come all the way... t-to talk to me? Um, right now, I'm a bit... err, I mean, yes, I'm available! I'm available, but I can't... Sorry...!
601040.feeling1: Keep your distance from me! Shoo, shoo...!!
601040.propose: Wh-what should I be saying during a wedding ceremony? ...Um, I don't need to say anything at all? Well then... *kiss* Th-that's fine too, right...?
601040.profile: I am the name ship of the Maestrale-class destroyers, Maestrale. During that war, I remember hitting a naval mine and having to return to port for repairs... The rest of my history? Umm, I, I don't think there's anything else...
601040.mission: Are you going to... continue working on your high-priority missions? Err, I mean... let, let me help you!
601040.home: How to make tea... Um, take the teabag and steep it in hot water... Commander, p-please let it sit for a few minutes...
601040.win_mvp: My thoughts about getting MVP? ......Uh, umm, it's nice...?
601040.expedition: A commission has been completed. The dockhead is looking rather crowded...
couple_encourage: Libeccio, w-w-wait for me...!
601040.mail: The mail, where'd I put the mail...? Phew, I almost forgot it after all the time I spent organizing it...
601040.feeling3: Commander... Please look over this. It's a table of our recent mission earnings... I hope it can be of help to you...
601040.lose: I've been defeated... What should I be saying...?

900184.detail: Want to look at my medal collection?
900184.login: You've come. If it's fighting, I'm ready for it any time.
900184.feeling2: It is my wish to live honestly and sincerely. That's why I'll speak my mind if I have something to say. You too should do the same without holding back.
900184.main: Is it you, Commander? ...Recently, I'm thinking about whether or not I can engage in anti-submarine actions...|Luck is also a part of strength? Then if possible, I'd like to impart some of it to my older sister.|So long as we live, there are things that will never go our way. When we die, it must happen in a way that carries no regrets.
900184.feeling5: What do you want to do after the war? --Me? I'll probably stick with you. I feel the safest out of battle when I'm with you. Will you... take me along with you?
900184.upgrade: I will show you... what lies at the end of power
900184.unlock: Second ship of the Yorktown class, Enterprise, reporting for duty. I will neither sympathize nor hold back with my enemies, and instead, I go all out. Such is my way.
900184.feeling4: There's no meaning in being peerless. As long as you are here, Commander, I can draw upon all of my strength. Let us end this war.
900184.feeling1: ...Commander, you don't seem to have enough courage
900184.propose: I carry with me the hopes and wills of the countless battlefields and goodbyes that I have experienced. Commander, are you prepared to shoulder them all? …I see. Then let us walk together until the end of our lives.
900184.drop_descrip: Yorktown-class aircraft carrier ー Enterprise, Hull Number CV-6!
900184.profile: I am the Yorktown class aircraft carrier, Enterprise. "Grey Ghost" is one of the many nicknames I have. My smoke-covered and bloodstained battle record is a reminder of my mission. I will continue to be victorious until the war ends.
900184.mission: Commander, your missions are not yet completed.  Hurry up and set off!
900184.home: It's one battle after another, huh...
900184.win_mvp: Commander, tell me. How many more do I have to sink?
900184.expedition: I've been on the battlefield for a long time, so I know about the importance of logistics. Commander, let's greet the girls who work hard behind the scenes.
couple_encourage: Teaming up with old rivals doesn't feel so bad.
Time to show you the true meaning of invincibility!
Such a playful old partner!
Brave Eagles, we fight until the end!
Heh, want to square off against me?
We all know each other. Come on, let's go!
900184.feeling3: All the lights in the sky are stars, just as all the lights on the seas are enemies... Commander, will there be a day where there's no more fighting?
900184.lose: I've lost after giving my all. I'm not regretting this...

301411.detail: Getting changed is a pain, but since everyone wanted to see me in a costume, I did it... Hip, hop.
301411.touch: Commander, are you scared of zombies?
301411.login: Commander? If you don't give me taiyaki, I'll summon Minazuki~
301411.main: Bouncing around is exhausting. Commander, your lap please. |Halloween is all about witches, pumpkins, and... delicious taiyaki! Ommfh!|If the seal on my head gets removed, I'll turn into a real zombie... That's what Minazuki said, anyway.
301411.unlock: Mikazuki is supposed to be... a zombie? Um... hip... hop... Commander, trick or treaaaaat~
301411.drop_descrip: Mikazuki is supposed to be... a jiangshi? Um... hip... hop... Commander, trick or treaaaaat~
301411.touch2: My outfit is all messed up now... even though it took so long to put on...
301411.home: I got so much candy... Mutsuki seems to really like them, so I'll give it all to her later.

101461.detail: I've got bunny pajamas on top of a bunny girl costume. That's double the bunny right there.
101461.touch: You want a bubblegum kiss? Sure. I've got plenty of flavors you can choose from.
101461.login: Heya. Wanna play a game? Mobile, console, or tabletop?
101461.headtouch: It's only human to want to touch the bun, I guess.
101461.main: Meowfficer plushes, Manjuu hand puppets... I never realized how much weird stuff I've amassed over the years.|I invited Laffey over, thinking she'd be fun to chill with. Turns out she's just a sleep junkie, like Nicholas. |Yeah, the place is a mess, but I'm used to it. It's way too much work to tidy up, so let's not.
101461.unlock: Welcome to my private retreat, where you can skip work and veg out all you want. And by "skip work" I mean "enjoy your regularly scheduled day off." Anyway, make yourself at home, Commander.
101461.drop_descrip: Welcome to my private retreat, where you can skip work and veg out all you want. And by "skip work" I mean "enjoy your regularly scheduled day off." Anyway, make yourself at home, Commander.
101461.touch2: I'm starting to think this outfit is a bit too inviting...
101461.home: Oh, there's that collector's edition I ordered. What to do with these stickers... Guess I'll put 'em somewhere.
101461.mail: Oh, new mail. Let's see here... Figures. This one's for you, Commander.

301660.detail: I feel a little sad when I see planes in the air... But it's okay, that's all in the past. What's more important is keeping my chin up and smiling. Right, Commander?
301660.touch: Mmh... I try not to think about why we all got separated. Besides, we got to reunite here, so let's instead live our lives happily ever after.
301660.login: You don't find my appearance odd? I feel the best way to greet someone is with a smile!
301660.battle: Everyone, try to avoid getting hurt if you can...
301660.hp_warning: You must remain calm in the face of danger. Don't worry about me.
301660.feeling2: I'd like to get to know you, Commander. *Giggle*, what should we start with?
301660.mission_complete: A mission has been completed. You did a great job, Commander!
301660.main: Asashio and I have always been together. Yup, we even sleep in the same bed. She's so quiet when she's sleeping.|We might not always be able to stick together, but we'd never leave anyone behind... That's why this place feels like home to me.|I've made you some tea. Take your time to savor it. By the way, is my tea-making ability to your liking?
301660.feeling5: We're all to ourselves now. My heart's been thumping for some time now... Commander, could we huddle up next to each other, just for a little while?
301660.upgrade: Now it'll be easier for me to avoid getting hurt. Thank you, Commander.
301660.unlock: Destroyer Arashio, here to join your fleet. I'll provide everyone with the support they need~
301660.feeling4: It's gotten quite late... But I really enjoyed chatting with you! Say, don't your shoulders get stiff from sitting down all day? Would you like a massage?
301660.feeling1: Oh, Asashio? There there, there's nothing to be afraid of... You'll have to excuse me, I need to stay with Asashio.
301660.propose: Commander, I won't say anything indecent, but there's one thing I want to tell you... Umm... I'll always be there to support you. Your side is the place where I truly belong.
301660.skill: I'll keep everyone out of harm's way.
301660.profile: I am Arashio, the fourth Asashio-class destroyer. I was part of Destroyer Division 8 along with Ooshio, Michishio, and of course Asashio. Lastly... I hope I can stay with everyone this time around.
301660.touch2: Eeeeek! ... Is this truly necessary to become an adult?
301660.mission: New missions have appeared. I'll gladly help you with them, Commander.
301660.home: Stellar work, Commander. Would you like to rest your head in my lap?
301660.win_mvp: Why, I'm the MVP...? Hmm, this might not be so bad.
301660.expedition: Commander, I believe the commission team has returned. Let us head over to receive them.
couple_encourage: Destroyer Division 8, let's all stick together now.
Asashio, I'm right by your side. Don't be scared.
301660.mail: You've received mail. Shall we go see what it is, Commander?
301660.feeling3: Did you have another nightmare? Aww, relax, Commander, everything will be okay.
301660.lose: There's no need to worry, we'll win the next time!

105029.touch: Hmm? What's up, Commander? Do you need my help? Sure~ just leave it to me!
105029.login: Howdy, Commander~ Are you doin' well?
105029.main: Commander, how about we hold a Fleet Problem? I'm pretty good at those~ |Commander, wanna go riding with me? We can both ride the same horse, hehe~ |Hey Commander, you gotta hear this! I just scored a win against my sister! Yaaay~!
105029.unlock: Thanks a ton, Commander. With my new strength, do you think I've managed to catch up to my sister a little? Ehehe, for your sake, I'll work even harder!
105029.drop_descrip: Thanks a ton, Commander. With my new strength, do you think I've managed to catch up to my sister a little? Ehehe, for your sake, I'll work even harder!
105029.home: I've already become more independent, so my sister told me that I'll be able to take care of you now! Ehehe~

202241.detail: Oh, is it that time already? I've prepared a few simple dishes. Commander, shall we invite the others to join us?
202241.login: I didn't think this swimsuit stood out, so I was surprised when you still found me right away...
202241.battle: You dare disturb the Commander's vacation? You won't get away with that.
202241.main: The sea is a tempestuous battlefield, and yet the beach is a relaxing Eden. What an incredible duality.|Beach volleyball? I've heard it's quite fun. Do you think I could give it a try?|The sand is so soft, so fine. It feels so pleasant between my toes...
202241.unlock: Sorry to keep you waiting, Commander. Thank you very much for taking me on vacation. Standing in front of you like this... is a little embarrassing... Nevertheless, what do you think of... my swimsuit?
202241.drop_descrip: Sorry to keep you waiting, Commander. Thank you very much for taking me on vacation. Standing in front of you like this... is a little embarrassing... Nevertheless, what do you think of... my swimsuit?
202241.touch2: Commander, the others are still here.
202241.home: What's wrong, Commander? Are you still preoccupied with work?
202241.mail: It's the mail? Don't tell me our vacation is over already...

601041.detail: Though I'm not able to build the Colosseum like Lady Veneto can, when it comes to the Leaning Tower, a cathedral, or a basilica... Um, I can kind of get the rough shape down!
601041.login: Greetings, greetings... Err, umm, Commander, w-want to sit down?
601041.main: Veneto's Colosseum is truly spectacular... I wish I could fill in the other half...|Libeccio, stop trying to drag me around.. You can go hang out with the commander instead.|The letters I etch into the sand are immediately washed away by the waves. I see, this is what they mean when they say "write your worries on the beach"...
601041.unlock: It's way too crowded on the beach... I'd much rather be– Oh, Commander? Are you not good with crowded places either...?
601041.drop_descrip: It's way too crowded on the beach... I'd much rather be– Oh, Commander? Are you not good with crowded places either...?
601041.touch: Commander, did you want to get buried in the sand just like these manjuu? I'll see what I can do then...
601041.home: Commander, did you come all the way here to see me? Th-thanks for your concern...

301661.detail: The shimmering of fireworks reflected across the water's surface... How enchanting and ephemeral...
301661.touch: Commander, I'm really glad I get to enjoy fireworks with you and the others~
301661.login: Commander, do you like fireworks? In that case, I'll help you light some~
301661.main: Sparklers might not be as gorgeous as the fireworks that blossom in the sky, but it's nice to be able to have something you can enjoy at your own pace.|Asashio, will you be able to remember this place? Try not to get lost, okay?|It's so quiet along the river bank... You can even hear the soft crackling of fireworks.
301661.unlock: Looks like you found me, Commander. Hehe, want to light some fireworks with me? Spending time together should be more fun than being alone, right?
301661.drop_descrip: Looks like you found me, Commander. Hehe, want to light some fireworks with me? Spending time together should be more fun than being alone, right?
301661.touch2: Eek... Are you doing this because there are no people nearby...?
301661.home: Is this... a new sparkler? Thanks, Commander~

702060.detail: How do you like my tails? They're super fluffy and feel nice in your hands~ By the way, I made them myself♪
702060.touch: Hmmhm~♪ Oh, do you want to chat? Why, sure thing!
702060.login: Good morning. Sorry that I'm late, I ran into a friend along the way and stopped to have a chat.
702060.battle: I'll open fire on the enemy~
702060.hp_warning: Aww, these tails took a lot of work to make...
702060.feeling2: I might not have many special skills to boast about, but I'll do my best to live up to your hopes~
702060.mission_complete: Mission complete~ Now let's tackle another job while we're in high spirits~
702060.main: Are we going on a rescue mission today? I really love helping people~|Pirouette and a spin~ To my right is a fox, and a bunny to the left~♪|Whew... Hmm~♪ Staaare... Aha!
702060.feeling5: Today is my watch-only day, but tomorrow we can chat to our heart's content. This should fix our little time-schedule problem~ ...It doesn't make much difference in the end? Oh, I see...
702060.unlock: Zdravstuvuyte, Comrade~ I'm the Omaha-class light cruiser, Milwaukee, reporting for duty~ Oh, did I slip up? ...Ahaha, sure did. I'm Murmansk, from the Northern Parliament. It's a pleasure to meet you~
702060.feeling4: Hmmhm~♪ Once I start chatting with you, it's really hard to stop~ Is that a problem for you, in regards to work? Aww, that's a shame...
702060.feeling1: Is there something wrong? I'm worried about you...
702060.propose: Taking this oath means we will share an eternal bond, right~? Wonderful! Then from this day forward, I promise I will see you every day, without it causing you any trouble~
702060.profile: I'm the light cruiser Murmansk. In terms of my history, I used to be an Omaha-class cruiser, doing rescue and escort missions. Then after becoming part of the Northern Parliament, I took part in some training missions~
702060.touch2: Ummm, I've got just a teensy qualm about you touching me this way...
702060.mission: You've still got missions~ Would you like me to pester you about them the next time you forget?
702060.home: Good to see you back~ I've left a refreshing drink and a juicy tangerine on your desk~
702060.win_mvp: We won~! Fighting comes naturally to me~
702060.expedition: The team has come back~ Should we offer them a few warming shots of vodka?
702060.feeling3: Oops, sorry, I lost track of time while chatting with a friend, and I forgot I was meeting with you today... Did I make you feel sad? I'm really sorry.
702060.lose: We lost the battle... I'm sorry for messing up...

601030.detail: Anything GB can help you with? I'm the oldest among my siblings and can do absolutely anything! Go on, let's hear it!
601030.touch: Huh? I've not done anything weird, have I?
601030.login: It's the start of a lively day! Keep at it, Commander! I-I'd better get ready for work too!
601030.battle: Rest easy knowing I won't let you down, Commander!
601030.feeling2: Hmm... I wonder how long it'll be before I become a fine lady like Veneto...
601030.headtouch: H-hey! I've grown out of headpats! They don't work on me, nuh-uh!
601030.mission_complete: Mission completed. Now where's the rewards report?
601030.main: S-Simoom isn't around here, is she? Ahem! Not to imply I'm afraid of her, my question simply stems from a sincere desire for amity and courtliness.|Oh goodness! Seriously, could you not pull weird faces while I'm trying to work?|Commander, would you care for a delectable dessert? I personally recommend tiramisu!
601030.feeling5: If you and I had met under different circumstances, like as classmates... then maybe we'd be in a typical romantic relationship... J-just thinking out loud, that's all!
601030.upgrade: One step closer to blooming into a gorgeous signorina!
601030.unlock: I am Vincenzo Gioberti of Sardegna! ...Eh, my name's hard to remember? ...Hmm, how about just "GB" then? That's a bit easier, right?
601030.feeling4: You only find my floundering endearing and cute because you make me flounder so much! ...Th-th-that said, I'm perfectly fine with being called c-cute...
601030.feeling1: Sadly, there's no cure for your chronic hopelessness, Commander.
601030.propose: You want to... get engaged with me?! B-b-b-but I...! Calm down, GB! Don't get too excited, be cool and graceful like a big sister and respond with grazia! Okay, now... I say, Commander, would you be a darling and put the ring on my finger?
601030.profile: I'm Vincenzo Gioberti, the second Alfredo Oriani-class destroyer. I stood shoulder-to-shoulder with valiant cruisers in many battles across– Huh? That's not quite right? Okay, my completion was a bit behind, but I was second to be launched among my siblings, so I do qualify as a bona fide big sister!
601030.touch2: Whuah?! You're a real creep, Commander...
601030.mission: Hm? New mission directives? But I'm not ready yet... Oh, they're not for me?
601030.home: How about a victory hug for everyone? Would that make me seem more mature?
601030.win_mvp: Hehe, easy as pizza pie! Err, I mean... Of course, just as expected! Nothing to get excited over!
couple_encourage: You don't need to be so formal with me, you know.
*gasp*! W-we're on the same side now, right...?
601030.mail: Here, I brought your mail, Commander.
601030.feeling3: I was born in the historic port of Livorno, a dreamy city on the gorgeous Sardegnian west coast! You should visit it with me if you ever get the chance, Commander!
601030.lose: Dangit... You won't discourage me so easily!

102121.detail: Y-you want to eat lunch together? Really? I bet you're just teasing me. Or are you... just hoping to get a taste of Helena's cooking?
102121.touch: It's small, but it's the only umbrella I could find. S-so, when 2 people are sharing it... i-it's only natural they'd have to stand so close together...
102121.main: I made a friend at school. He's brown, cuddly, and doesn't say a word, though...|There's nobody who's like you at school. Nobody who sometimes makes me laugh, sometimes makes me cry, and sometimes... Gosh, what am I saying...|nil
102121.unlock: If everyone's focusing on the teacher, they probably won't stare at me from up front... As for the umbrella, it's... I know it makes me stand out, but I don't want people to stare at me from behind either...
102121.drop_descrip: If everyone's focusing on the teacher, they probably won't stare at me from up front... As for the umbrella, it's... I know it makes me stand out, but I don't want people to stare at me from behind either...
102121.touch2: I-I don't have anything going for me besides my bust anyway...
102121.home: Don't say you'll "see me after school"... O-or else I'll just stay behind...

202242.detail: Too much sitting wears out one's legs. Stretching out like this... Aahhh, yes, that's much better.
202242.touch: Mmm... why not stretch out with me, Commander?
202242.login: Commander, welcome home. Ooh, I just realized. I should probably be saying "Happy Lunar New Year," shouldn't I?
202242.main: Commander... Do you enjoy such nostalgic music?|Hah... How should I spend this holiday? I think listening to music like this is quite nice... Aahh...|It's a holiday. No need to move, no need to fight... Now why not make every day a holiday?
202242.unlock: A "qipao," is it? So this legendary dress from the Dragon Empery... Putting it on and enjoying some nostalgic music, makes me... Ahhh... Commander, might we relax like this a bit longer...?
202242.drop_descrip: A "qipao," is it? This legendary dress from the Dragon Empery... Putting it on and enjoying some nostalgic music, makes me... Ahhh... Commander, might we relax like this a bit longer...?
202242.home: The kitchen sure seems busy. What's going on... in there?
202242.mail: Mail call... Must be some festival greetings? You're quite popular, Commander.

102059.detail: St. Louis always praises me like, "my, how you've grown" whenever I do anything... It's kind of embarrassing...
102059.login: Welcome back, Commander. Let's get to work and do our best.
102059.main: You want to know what my new and improved SG is capable of? All right... Find a place to hide that nobody knows about. Hehehe~|I think everyone would be better off living in the present without regrets than spend every day anxious about the future.|It's not enough to focus only on improving my equipment. I need to become stronger to use it properly, too.
102059.feeling5: I feel a bit more confident in myself when I'm with you, Commander. But I want more; I want to be the girl you rely on so I can be the center of your attention... It might be selfish to ask, but... will you love me?
102059.unlock: This new equipment... might take some time to get used to... N-no, I'm sure I can handle it now! Commander, Helena will... meet your expectations!
102059.drop_descrip: This new equipment... might take some time to get used to... N-no, I'm sure I can handle it now! Commander, Helena will... meet your expectations!
102059.touch2: You really can't go around doing this, Commander!
102059.win_mvp: Don't get complacent, Helena... You've got to get even stronger!
102059.expedition: SG receiving message... A commission team has returned to port.
102059.lose: It's okay, Helena. There's always next time...!

102253.detail: Beauty is fleeting. Look away for one moment, and you'll miss it forever... It's not exclusive to fireworks, either. When you see a thing of beauty, keep your eyes on it, Commander.
102253.touch: Fancy my dress? You can have a closer look at it all you want later.
102253.login: There you are, Commander! They're putting on a fireworks display tonight. Come with me and we'll check it out.
102253.main: Even in the cold winter, the thrill of watching fireworks with your friends warms you up. Ahahahah!|Being here with my sisters, us all watching the fireworks together... It's actually pretty nice.|Seeing these stunning fireworks makes me hope next year will go smoothly. Fingers crossed, Commander!
102253.unlock: I heard that this place is famous for its festivals with beautiful fireworks, so I made sure to come dressed for the occasion... What do you think? ...I'm even more beautiful? Well, I couldn't let the fireworks be the only things leaving an impression upon you tonight! Ahaha, just kidding~
102253.drop_descrip: I heard that this place is famous for its festivals with beautiful fireworks, so I made sure to come dressed for the occasion... What do you think? ...I'm even more beautiful? Well, I couldn't let the fireworks be the only things leaving an impression upo
102253.touch2: ...You wanna make like a firework and go bang, or what?

601032.detail: You may drink to your heart's content today! Worry not, just put it on my tab! ...Huh? The drinks were free to begin with?
601032.touch: Fare un brindisi! Indeed, this is how a signorina raises a toast.
601032.login: A refill, if you would, Manjuu waiter! Likewise for the Commander's glass, please! Now let me just... Hup... Ugh, these bar stools are sure are tall...
601032.main: This "for adults only" drink has gott my attention... Could I at least have a taste?|Commander, as this is an informal gathering, you are free to say whatever you please! I am a grown lady, and I can handle it!|We have some lovely tiramisu resting on the counter, Libeccio! Call over Maestrale and we'll all savor it together!
601032.unlock: "To refuse a fair signorina's invitation would be most uncouth"... Hehe~ Now, Commander, would you like to partake in some refreshments? Rest assured, they're all non-alcoholic♪
601032.drop_descrip: "To refuse a fair signorina's invitation would be most uncouth"... Hehe~ Now, Commander, would you like to partake in some refreshments? Rest assured, they're all non-alcoholic♪
601032.touch2: You'll never receive another party invitation from me again!
601032.home: I'm a signorina – I do of course understand if you're too busy for pleasantries, Commander. Having said that... You should at least tell me before you go out, all right?

701061.detail: Pamiat Merkuria is way above my skill level... Oh, I know! Commander, practice with me so I can get better!
701061.touch: O-one more round! If you win this one, then I'll get up and do work!
701061.login: Whoa! When'd you come in here, Commander? Never mind, let's just play video games!
701061.main: Whew, I'm tired! I'm gonna put on my sleep mask and catch some z's! ...Dang, not happening?|Rekordny! An Shan! I know you've got games in your room! You can try to hide your power level, but you're also a gamer, aren't you?|I learned a ton of gaming trivia from Pamiat Merkuria!
701061.unlock: It sucks not being able to play in the snow... Oh well! I'll play some games instead! Commander, let's play something fun together!
701061.drop_descrip: It sucks not being able to play in the snow... Oh well! I'll play some games instead! Commander, let's play something fun together!
701061.home: *yaaawn*... Hm? What time is it? Eh, guess I'll boot up the console and play something... Wait, no! I've gotta get eady for work!
701061.expedition: The commission team's back. Uh-huh... Okay, okay! I'll do it next time, I promise, just go and greet them this time for me! Please!

101260.battle: Don't like it, but will try my best.
101260.feeling2: ...Commander, lap. (Eldridge is trying to sit on your lap... while she's emitting sparks!)
101260.mission_complete: Commander... Rewards, edible? (Eldridge's eyes are sparkling with excitement.)
101260.main: Commander, hungry. Want food.|Commander, look! I can emit sparks!|Commander, fly. (Eldridge raises her arms up towards you.)
101260.feeling5: Commander, hug. (Eldridge is coming to you with her arms open. She's not emitting sparks.)
101260.feeling4: ... Commander, like. (Eldridge jumps onto you the moment she sees you. Let's just accept this display of straight-up affection!)
101260.feeling1: ... Commander, hate! (Eldridge is emitting sparks from her body to prevent you from approaching her.)
101260.drop_descrip: Cannon-class Destroyer Escort - Eldridge, Hull Number DE-173!
101260.profile:
Eldridge, Cannon-class destroyer escort.
Love snacks. Emit sparks.
Can't teleport...
101260.touch2: ... (Eldridge's expression hasn't changed, but her hair is charging up to shock you.)
101260.mission: Mission...! (Eldridge's hair sticking out from the top of her head forms an exclamation mark.)
101260.expedition: (Eldridge's hair is pointing at the door. It seems the girls who went on a commission have returned.)
couple_encourage: ... You don't like... to talk... either?
101260.mail: (A newly arrived letter is floating beside Eldridge) Brought mail!
101260.feeling3: ... Commander, fly. (Eldridge is looking at you like she wants you to pick her up, but she's emitting sparks!)

401011.detail: Bringing weapons to school is merely for self-defense purposes. There are always some bold fool who wishes to taunt Z1-sama!
401011.touch: Naturally, only the Commander can be called my most desirable partner!
401011.main: The homework was finished in a flash, hehe, naturally for my Z1-sama! |I did not break classroom rules! It’s just that the teacher is too boring, I recommend to everyone that I should teach the class, then... |Hehehe, stuff written on books may not always be correct!
401011.unlock: Because she’s the Z1, her results will of course be NO.1! Hehe, no matter where she goes, Z1-sama will always be the best!
401011.drop_descrip: Because she’s the Z1, her results will of course be NO.1! Hehe, no matter where she goes, Z1-sama will always be the best!
401011.touch2: People say when your head is pointed by a gun, your brain starts spinning. Commander, care to have a try?

101330.detail: What is it? Do you want something from me?
101330.login: Umm... What are we doing today, again?
101330.battle: I'll fight with all I've got!
101330.feeling2: Whuah! A-a plane came flying towards me! ... What? Th-that was just a beetle...?
101330.mission_complete: Mission complete! ... Did I do it right?
101330.main: If I stay out of sight, the Commander probably won't notice I'm neglecting my work...|Uughh... Following a schedule is so boooring! I say we do stuff when we see it needs doing! ... What? That's not gonna fly?|I've got a bunch of sisters, both younger and older than me! I forget their names all the time, though...
101330.feeling5: For whatever reason, I don't feel that scared of planes anymore. It's got to be because we love each other, Commander! ... At least that's what Thatcher told me. She's not wrong, is she?
101330.upgrade: Huh? Will this make me stronger?
101330.unlock: I'm Bush, from the Fletcher class! I'll be staying here from now on!
101330.feeling4: Gotcha! ... Well, how do you like the prank Thatcher taught me, Commander? ... Huh? But I thought you liked pranks, or at least Thatcher said that you do...
101330.feeling1: You need to learn to smile, Commander...
101330.propose: Does this mean you love me more than anyone else? If so, will you do anything I ask you to? Okay! I want some snacks from that store that jus opened, so let's go there right now!
101330.drop_descrip: Fletcher-class destroyer – Bush, Hull Number DD-529.
101330.profile: I'm the Fletcher-class destroyer Bush. Like my sisters, I fought in the Pacific Ocean and took on tons of missions! ... Planes? I-I don't wanna talk about those scary things!
101330.touch2: It's not okay to touch me like that!
101330.mission: You've got some missions left to do. Commander, you're not... slacking off again, are you?
101330.expedition: Oh, it's time to go welcome the commission team back!
101330.mail: I've brought your mail along! What does it say?
101330.feeling3: You know, I'm actually quite athletic! Check it out, I could hop side to side all day! ... *Pant*, *pant*... This is exhausting... I can't hop anymore...
101330.lose: Nooo! Get those planes away from meee!

201250.detail: Do you need anything? Or are you just here to chat?
201250.touch: What, you want to nuzzle against my lap? You can keep your fantasies in your dreams where they belong.
201250.login: Do you know how long you've kept me waiting, Commander? What's the meaning of this?
201250.battle: We must face our enemies seriously, no matter who they are.
201250.feeling2: Commander, while we're not that familiar with each other, I wouldn't take issue with having tea and chatting with you.
201250.mission_complete: Commander, our rewards have arrived. Well done, I say.
201250.main: I hate it when others underestimate me because of my size!|No one knows what's on a person's mind if they don't say it aloud. I do not like people who are roundabout.|I wish you would compliment me for being honest, rather than for being "cute." Not that I mind compliments like that.
201250.feeling5: Commander, I'm a straightforward person, and I'd like my partner to be as well. So be open-hearted and simply say what's on your mind. In return, I will be sincere with you as well.
201250.upgrade: I will not let your efforts go to waste.
201250.unlock: Are you the Commander? My name is Jersey, and don't you forget it.
201250.feeling4: But that's all right. You may fancy me if you like, but if you don't, then it's... not *not* a problem...
201250.feeling1: You are a halfhearted and lousy individual.
201250.propose: Now that I think about it, we've been so straightforward that we've not even done anything romantic... But now at least we know each other better than anyone else. I say we let romance into our lives starting today.
201250.skill: Now's not the time to be taking it easy!
201250.profile: I'm Jersey, of the J class. While I have neither noble blood nor a particularly outstanding combat record, my personality is what it is, so spare me your complaints. What happened in Malta was just a slipup. But, admittedly, mistakes are mistakes. That much I know.
201250.touch2: C-Commander?! I-I-I appreciate your straightforwardness, but now isn't the time...
201250.mission: Stop pretending like you haven't seen the new missions and get them done already.
201250.home: Don't overexert yourself after returning from the battlefield. Relax.
201250.win_mvp: This is the might of the J class! Regret your own carelessness!
201250.expedition: Commander, a commission is done. You haven't forgotten about it, have you?
couple_encourage: Everyone, try to keep up!
201250.mail: Your mail, Commander. Don't forget to read it.
201250.feeling3: There is one thing I want to set straight with you; I'm not foul-mouthed, I simply say what's on my mind. For instance... do you have a thing for little children?
201250.lose: Ugh... You will pay dearly for staining my dress! Know this!

105030.detail: Thanks. This is the first time someone has really cared about me...
105030.touch: You dont have to get worked up over tiny things, Commander.
105030.login: Commander, you know you can always share any thoughts you have with me.
105030.feeling2: You and Arizona can hide behind me. I'll protect you.
105030.mission_complete: I left your rewards over there. Don't forget to collect them!
105030.main: Your eyes... Why do they look like those of an abandoned puppy?|Can you please not look at me with those hungry eyes?|You don't have the best imagination, do you?
105030.feeling5: Mmm, you've worked so hard. I didn't think that you'd be able to catch up with me... You want a reward? How about a kiss? Or an unforgettable evening? Both are fine with me~!
105030.unlock: I'm Pennsylvania, lead ship of an improved Nevada class. You can call me "Sister Penn." I've sortied on countless successful missions, so you can be confident in my ability.
105030.feeling4: It's alright if you don't want to push yourself further. You've worked very hard. I thought you were joking, but... How do I say this... I'm used to protecting others... But to meet someone who cares about me really is something else.
105030.propose: This fleet has turned into a place I can call home... The people I want to protect, and the person who protects me despite being unable to kill a bug, and then the 'me' who becomes so giddy for that person are all here... You idiot *blush*...
105030.drop_descrip: Pennsylvania-class battleship –  Pennsylvania, Hull Number BB-38!
105030.skill: Is that the best you've got?
105030.profile: I'm Pennsylvania, lead ship of an improved Nevada class. You can call me "Sister Penn." I really shouldn't brag, but I've sortied on countless successful missions. You can definitely depend on me!
105030.touch2: ...!! Hold up, are you alright in the head?
105030.mission: I say, have you forgotten a mission?
105030.home: Having a drink after battle is something else. You want some?
105030.win_mvp: Tsk...Winning like this is so dull...
105030.expedition: Commission completed... Not bad. Everyone seems to be growing stronger.
couple_encourage: As an adult, let me protect you!
105030.mail: Here, I got your mail. Will ya make sure to reply soon?
105030.feeling3: You want to stand next to me?... Think carefully now. That is a very hard thing to do.
105030.lose: I was a fool to have any expectations of your commanding abilities.

107140.detail: Sigh... The last exercise revealed a lot of problems... Commander?! Please, could you please knock before entering a lady's room?
107140.touch: You shouldn't slack off, Commander. Oh my, am I the distracting you from your work? Heheh, just kidding~♪
107140.login: Oh my, you don't look that great... How about I do something special for you? What, you ask? Hehe, why don't you try imagining what it might be?
107140.hp_warning: Hard to port! Watch out for fire!
107140.feeling2: You're going to head out on patrol? Then... wrap your arm around mine, just like this~ Oh, do you dislike me, Commander? Or... are you worried about the other girls' reactions?
107140.mission_complete: Great job completing those missions! You're quite something, Commander!
107140.main: What's on the moon, you wonder? A rabbit? Aliens? Hehe. Whatever it is, I'd like to see it for myself one day.|If you're tired, you can snuggle up to me and rest for a bit. Oh, would you rather have a lap pillow instead? Well, if someone walks in on us, I'll leave the explanations to you~ Hehe.|The files are organized, and the Commander's schedule is ready... Phew... I should be fine.
107140.feeling5: I'm not particularly noteworthy as a warship, and it might be a while until I can truly stand by your side as your equal... Even so, are you really fine with me? Can I really stay at your side?
107140.unlock: Hi there~ I'm Ticonderoga, the newest arrival at your port. Hmm, you look just as friendly as they said you'd be~ Thank goodness. So, how about a hug to start us off on the right foot? Hehe~
107140.feeling4: For some reason, it seems there are some strange rumors about the two of us floating about... Just as planned? ...Commander!
107140.feeling1: It seems I won't be able to save the Commander with my efforts alone...
107140.propose: Huh?! Uh, umm... What am I supposed to say in response to your proposal...? Uhh... You're really giving this to me? Ahh, I'm sorry, I'm just so happy that my heart is about to explode and I don't know what to do and ahh...
107140.drop_descrip: Essex-class aircraft carrier – Ticonderoga, Hull Number CV-14.
107140.skill: Let's show off the fruits of our labor!
107140.profile: The sixth ship in the Essex-class, and the first in the class to have a long hull. I was once called "Hancock," but in the end, I was renamed to "Ticonderoga" in commemoration of the great war. That's about it.
107140.touch2: My, are you sure you want to be doing this? I think I saw Aoba or someone passing by with a camera earlier.
107140.mission: You still haven't completed the new missions? Hmm... Well, it's fine for now. Just take care of them at your own pace.
107140.home: Good work on the operation, Commander. Give me your arm... Good, there we go. Hehe, doesn't it feel nice? Let all the fatigue dissipate, just like that!
107140.win_mvp: Oh, we won. It's because you were by our side, Commander.
107140.expedition: The commissions team is back. We should go and greet them right away.
couple_encourage: Shall we show them our Essex-class synergy? Hehe~
Let's calm down and take this slowly!
107140.mail: There's some mail for you, Commander. You should check them as soon as possible. After all, it'd be a disaster if you overlooked something.
107140.feeling3: There are many excellent allies here at the port. I... I'll have to work hard, won't I~♪

900134.detail: Hmm, you want to know how well I fight?
900134.touch: Don’t touch me as if you’re trying to be intimate with me.
900134.login: Welcome back... how does my smile look? (Forcibly smiles)
900134.hp_warning: I won't let go of victories to my enemies!
900134.feeling2: What must I do to possess a good smile... think about the things I like? If so, I feel very happy even at the thought of winning against South Dakota... muahahaha...
900134.mission_complete: Go grab the reward yourself, I’m not interested.
900134.main: My smile looks beautiful? You jerk... oops, keep smiling, keep smiling. Thank you for your compliments. | Hey, that rigid South Dakota is still the same. Commander, you see, I am cuter than her. | A true measurement of friendship is their actions and not their words, I don’t like people who are rhetorical in nature.
900134.feeling5: I couldn’t help but smile when I saw you, this is the first time that I’m feeling this way... although, I also have other feelings rushing towards me. I suddenly want to see your expression when you are bullied by me—— Commander, stay with me for a while. (Laughs)
900134.upgrade: It feels so good to become stronger.
900134.unlock: Hello, Commander, I am Washington... my sister told me that I cannot be so rough once I join the fleet, so I am practicing my smile. Darn, why must I listen to her...
900134.feeling4: Lately, my smile has become more natural? Emm, huh (scratches head), I was recently trying to find a new hobby. While I was searching, I realized that being with you is not so bad… (whispers)
900134.feeling1: You are too weak, it’s no fun playing with you, go practice some more.
900134.propose: Wait wait! We’re doing “that”, right? Is this your new way of teasing me!... Damn, you bastard, I’m not sure if I should cry or laugh about this...
900134.drop_descrip: North Carolina class battleship— Washington, hull number BB-56.
900134.skill: Out of my way. I'm ready to fight!
900134.profile: North Carolina class ship no. 2. I am Washington! The thing I like to do the most is to destroy my enemies. Recently, I am practicing on my smile. —— Battle record? I don’t really show off with such things, all in all, how’s my smile?
900134.mission: A new mission? Haha, now my blood is boiling.
900134.home: I’m glad that you didn’t get hurt—— What?! I don’t have feelings for you!
900134.win_mvp: Sure enough, I am happiest when all the foes are annihilated~
900134.expedition: Your memory can’t be worse than mine, right? The commission fleet has returned, won’t you go greet them?
900134.feeling3: No, no, that’s not right. If we do it this way, won’t it end much the same like in the past? … Don’t try so hard? You sometimes say stuff like that… Hmm? That was a good smile from me just now?
900134.lose: Oh, I will not forget you!

607011.detail: Oh my, Commander~ If you stare so much at a young signorina's swimsuit, you're going to give others a bad impression~
607011.touch: My Commander, would you like some fruit?
607011.login: My Commander, would you like a floaty ring or a life jacket? ...You don't need either? I'll be taking them then~
607011.main: A swimsuit contest? My my, that sounds like one of Littorio's concoctions~ Don't worry, I'm not interested in entering.|Graf Zeppelin, huh... I don't think we have much in common after all...|I'd like to fly my planes around, but... No, I've got to practice some self-restraint...!
607011.unlock: Good day, my Commander. We have the day off to enjoy the sea breeze and the ocean waves~ Hehe, would you like to help yourself to some fruit?
607011.drop_descrip: Good day, my Commander. We have the day off to enjoy the sea breeze and the ocean waves~ Hehe, would you like to help yourself to some fruit?
607011.touch2: My Commander, after we get back, I'll need to lecture you on how to treat a signorina.
607011.home: I've already tidied up your schedule. Hehe, though it's your day off, I can still handle these small details~

102052.detail: In preparation for today, I got St. Louis to teach me how to dance. She laughed a lot at me, telling me I'm "such a klutz"... Ahah.
102052.touch: I'm all ready, Commander. Shall we dance?
102052.login: Commander, the party is about to start.
102052.main: Commander, you know something? It's thanks to you that I've become as cheerful as I am now. Ahah~|I'm not going to be scared or hesitate ever again because you and my friends are always with me.|My dance partner will be... No, it'll just be you, Commander. I have so many things I want to tell you.
102052.feeling5: You and my friends have always taken care of, looked after, and protected me. But that can't go on forever. I want to stand beside you and become someone people can count on... So, could you wait for me just a little longer... please?
102052.unlock: Um, Commander, could we... share a dance? I have things I want to tell you...
102052.drop_descrip: Um, Commander, could we... share a dance? I have things I want to tell you...
102052.touch2: Eek?! ... Ah, sorry, did I step on your foot, Commander?
102052.mission: Commander, please go complete your missions. Don't worry, I'll be here waiting for you.
102052.home: Commander, before we leave for the party, do you have any unfinished business?
102052.win_mvp: Yeah, that's right...! You're awesome, Helena!
102052.expedition: Commander, let's extend an invitation to the commission team to join us for the party.
102052.mail: It seems you've got an invitation to another dance party... Hahah, you really are a superstar, Commander.
102052.lose: It's okay, there's always next time...!

607012.detail: Did you enjoy my black tea? I've worked very, very hard so that I may meet your every demand~♪
607012.login: Mm, yes, that's just perfect... Oh my, Commander, how are you doing today? –Hmm, I added too much sugar...?
607012.main: Yummy treat~ Become sweet and replete~♪ Commander, I've prepared a little magic spell to make your tea that much tastier~♪|Shall we invite Carabiniere as well next time? I'm sure she'll be quite surprised~♪
607012.unlock: Oh, my Commander? I didn't expect to meet you here! Fortune smiles upon me today. Hehe~ If you have a minute to spare, would you care to join me for a cup of tea?
607012.drop_descrip: Oh, my Commander? I didn't expect to meet you here! Fortune smiles upon me today. Hehe~ If you have a minute to spare, would you care to join me for a cup of tea?
607012.touch2: Nngh–– Commander, I think this might be a little too naughty?
607012.home: Commander, would you like some Amaretti? I thought some sugar would be nice to help you replenish after leading a battle~♪

102122.detail: Commander, you're the one who messed with my cannons, didn't you? A-admit it! Admit it while you still have the chance...
102122.touch: You called over Helena?! This is NOT the way I want to make her laugh!
102122.battle: If I get rid of everyone who saw me... then I won't have anything to be embarrassed about!
102122.main: *Gasp*! Where the heck is all this water coming from?!|Commander, you don't sound convincing at all when you tell me my swimsuit is cute while you're laughing!|*Sob*... Everyone's going to laugh at me...
102122.unlock: Aaaahh! My sundae! What's up with this stupid hose?! Commander, don't just stand there, help me!
102122.drop_descrip: Aaaahh! My sundae! What's up with this stupid hose?! Commander, don't just stand there, help me!
102122.touch2: How could you, Commander... I'll hose you till you're as soaked as I am!
102122.home: C-Commander, umm, do you wanna take a cold shower...?
102122.win_mvp: Today was your unlucky day... because I'm in a REALLY bad mood!

202244.drop_descrip: Oh... Welcome, Commander. Can I take your order...? Or maybe, you just wanted to kick back and relax? ...Either way is fine with me.

202120.touch: Aimlessly touching a lady is not a gentlemanly behaviour. Please behave yourself around others.
202120.login: Welcome back, master. I've prepared the tea. Furthermore, I've sorted the documents over here. Please work at your leisure.
202120.battle: It's a maid's duty to remove their master's obstacles.
202120.hp_warning: Everyone, the main dish has yet to come!
202120.feeling2: I'm terribly sorry... I'm still new to this fleet, so I'm somewhat unfamiliar with my duties and cannot serve you at 100% capacity... Please look forward to my continued service.
202120.mission_complete: Your rewards have been delivered, Master.
202120.main: In order to become an excellent master, you must start from self confidence. Please do your best to turn your will into action, master.|Do you want some tea? Ah... if you want something else, I'll prepare some coffee or whiskey.|Sunbathing on Thames river wasn't bad. But this current life of mine is better...
202120.feeling5: Are you awake? ...Hehe, your sleeping face was so cute, I couldn't bear waking you up... How did it feel, resting on my lap? You are free to enjoy it to your heart's content
202120.unlock: Are you my master? Pleasure to meet you. I am Belfast the maid. From now on, I dedicate myself to you.
202120.feeling4: It is important to observe your intentions sensitively. Especially intentions that you yourself are not aware of, master... I'm mean, you say? Hehe. Recently I've come to enjoy your troubled look a little. By all means, please forgive me.
202120.feeling1: Correcting her master is also a maid's duty...
202120.propose: Now this is a little troubling... I'm fine with simply protecting you, my master, as well as occassionally enjoying your troubled look... But with such an important bond being formed, I've become wanting to serve you even more, as well as receiving more of your attention, master...
202120.drop_descrip: Edinburgh-Class light cruiser ー Belfast, Hull number C35!
202120.skill: Dear enemies, this is going to be a little bit painful
202120.profile: Good day to you. I am Belfast, the second ship of the Edinburgh class. I have duties as the head maid while being the Royal Navy's greatest cruiser. I had taken part in many battles, and borne witness to lady Scharnhorst's fall... Those are but the past for a maid. Please say something should you have a need for me.
202120.touch2: It's a maid's duty to dedicate her all to her master. Would you like to see, master?
202120.mission: A new mission has been given to us, master. Please confirm it.
202120.home: Welcome back, master. I've readied some light snacks over here.
202120.win_mvp: Oh my, I didn't spend as much effort as cleaning up a stain in a tablecloth.
202120.expedition: Master, the ladies who went off for commissions have been waiting for you to greet them.
202120.mail: There's a new letter. Shall I read it for you, master?
202120.feeling3: This is something I made using the connections I have to the fleet. Please have a taste -- Is the taste to your liking?
202120.lose: Please retreat first, master. I still have some matters to attend to.

702061.detail: I'm spending the whole day lazing around indoors, so I don't really need to get dressed~ You can change into loungewear too if you want, Commander~
702061.hp_warning: Oh gosh! Silly me, I need to focus...!
702061.main: Have you seen my favorite pillow? It's "just down pillow"...?|Apparently, Pamiat Merkuria likes lazing around too~ I find that surprising, but also kind of unsurprising at the same time...|Whew... I can't help but admire how well everyone's holding up in this snowy weather~
702061.unlock: ...Achoo! Uhh, good morning... Snow? Yeah, it is snowing today... Woah, it's really coming down hard... Ahaha~
702061.drop_descrip: ...Achoo! Uhh, good morning... Snow? Yeah, it is snowing today... Woah, it's really coming down hard... Ahaha~
702061.touch2: You won't find any tails down there today~
702061.home: Welcome back~! A warm beverage would be perfect right now~ Like vodka, perhaps?
702061.win_mvp: Easy as porridge in the morning~

301240.detail: Excellent. You seem to have remembered our appointment~
301240.touch: You want to touch my tail? Well, I can't promise you what happens next~
301240.login: Did you only just realize that you still have work to do?
301240.battle: Let's hurry up and get this done!
301240.hp_warning: Tsk... things didn't quite go as planned...
301240.feeling2: You wouldn't happen to have feelings for me, would you? Save your breath, there's not a chance in hell~
301240.mission_complete: Looks like nobody has noticed that the task rewards haven't been collected yet... Hehe, in that case...
301240.main: Are you more concerned with your popularity among the girls than with your actual work? |Yukikaze? I must admit, she is the luckier one... |Huh? Right now... could you not space out while we still have work to do?
301240.feeling5: Fine, fine, it's my loss~ I'll allow you to date me from now on. ... Don't tell me you don't even know how to date...?
301240.unlock: Oh my, what's with that scared expression? I won't bite~ I am Hatsushimo of the Hatsuharu class. I hope we can get along, ahaha~
301240.feeling4: What a stubborn fellow... Fine, I suppose I can give you a little reward. Here, this is the great Hatsushimo's lap pillow. Enjoy it while you can.
301240.feeling1: What a pity... You're not even worth making fun of anymore~
301240.propose: A ring? Hmph, are you trying to get back at me for all those times I mocked you? Too bad, I won't fall for that... Eh, seriously? W-w-wait, this isn't how the script is supposed to go... *blushes*
301240.skill: I'm being underestimated, whatever shall I do~?
301240.profile: I am Hatsushimo of the Hatsuharu-class destroyers. I fought in many battles alongside the 21st Destroyer Division. Although I didn't really sustain many injuries, in the end, you know how it went...
301240.touch2: Ehehe... Commander, such a brave soul...
301240.mission: Eeeh? Not even kids would leave those missions unfinished~ How lame!
301240.home: Good work, everyone... Huh, don't get me wrong, I didn't say you~
301240.expedition: I can't wait to see the icy faces of the girls who you stood up~
couple_encourage: Wakaba, be extra attentive when it's foggy.
301240.mail: There's mail for you. Shall I open it for you? Hehe, don't worry, I won't charge you a cent♪
301240.feeling3: Oh, so you plan to "capture" me? Give up already, it's no use~

101261.main: Commander, eat together... Christmas feast! |Commander, present? (Eldridge's hair twirls in anticipation)
101261.unlock: Merry Christmas... Commander, Eldridge's outfit... cute?
101261.drop_descrip: Merry Christmas... Commander, Eldridge's outfit... cute?

213041.detail: Trick or treat! Give me candy, or you'll taste one of my pranks! Although, even if you give me some... well, you'll see for yourself! Tee hee~
213041.touch: Shake hands with my Halloween Mark I! Come on, Mark I, show the Commander your special trick~!
213041.login: Tee hee~ Who knows where I've planted my pumpkin surprise~
213041.main: Take a gander at my Halloween Mark I! Looks cracking, doesn't it!|Nelson's wearing a Halloween costume?! Really?! Let me have a look at it, Commander!|If only we had more holidays where you could cause mischief and get away with it scot-free~
213041.unlock: Kabooom! You thought it was a pumpkin, but it was me, Abercrombie, with my Mark I! Commander, did I scare you senseless? Muahaha!
213041.drop_descrip: Kabooom! You thought it was a pumpkin, but it was me, Abercrombie, with my Mark I! Commander, did I scare you senseless? Muahaha!
213041.touch2: Taste the retribution of my Mark I! (Pow!)
213041.home: I wonder how people would react if they got my custom-made horseradish candy~ Tee hee~!

101331.detail: North Carolina asked me to paint a portrait of Washington smiling, but Washington didn't really wanna do it... I think I know why! Maybe smiling is embarrassing for her?
101331.touch: Hm? Do you want me to paint something for you, Commander?
101331.login: Aww, do we really have to work? I'm not done painting yet...
101331.main: Just give me a minute! I'm just finishing up my painting!|This is my sketchbook I use for drawing practice! And no looking inside, okay?|I'm gonna draw portraits of everyone at the port! Heehee!
101331.unlock: Tadaaah! All done! How does it look? I think I'm pretty talented as an artist!
101331.drop_descrip: Tadaaah! All done! How does it look? I think I'm pretty talented as an artist!
