101331.touch2: Oh no! I got paint on my clothes because of that!
101331.home: *gasp*! You spooked me... You almost made my hand slip and mess up my painting!

701071.detail: Gromky's looking for me? Ugh... I don't wanna go outside. But I'd feel bad about telling her to buzz off, and pretending to be sick would worry her... Hrmmm...
701071.touch: Want me to read aloud for you, or...?
701071.login: I got up to this part just the other day. Time to read the rest. Mm, that's all.
701071.main: If you wanna lounge around, do it over there. Mm, that's all.|Mmmh... *yaaaaawn*... Huh?! Oh no, don't tell me I dozed off... You didn't see anything, got it? I mean, of course you didn't!|Retivy... I mean, Tai Yuan, and I shared our recommended book lists. It turns out we've got pretty similar tastes. Heheh.
701071.feeling5: Wanna read this book with me, Commander? This one. It's called "The Happy Lovebirds." If we read it together, I might just be able to figure out what it's about. Mm, that's all.
701071.unlock: Wh-who gave you the right to just barge in? ...I did? Huh. Well, seeing as you're here, I guess we could read a book together. Mm, that's all.
701071.drop_descrip: Wh-who gave you the right to just barge in? ...I did? Huh. Well, seeing as you're here, I guess we could read a book together. Mm, that's all.
701071.touch2: I-I knew it! You are a creep...!
701071.mission: You could fill a whole book with all these unfinished mission drafts...
701071.home: So many books lying around... Oh, Commander, I could use your help returning these books to the shelf when you come back.
701071.mail: There's a letter for you. Can I keep the stamp? Mm, thanks.

399030.detail: Those who lead upon the battlefield must also carry their own blade... Worry not, this one is not heavy at all.
399030.touch: Being small has its advantages... Heheh. For example, don’t even try to hit me in a game of dodgeball!
399030.login: Commander, you’ve come. I am currently training this little one. Indeed, I must teach it to stand like a general.
399030.battle: The enemy’s movements... are clear as day! Everyone, follow me!
399030.hp_warning: It’s not wise to swim against the current... but we have no choice now!
399030.feeling2: Hmm, you’re curious about the little one...? Very well, perhaps I will give you a demonstration when I get the chance.
399030.mission_complete: Effort is rewarded in kind. Given how hard you’ve worked, Commander, your rewards won’t be disappointing.
399030.main: My Akizuki-class sisters have always taken good care of me. I, Kitakaze, swear to meet their expectations, and will work hard to protect everyone. |I prefer strategizing and leading from the rear over fighting in the frontlines... B-but I’m perfectly capable of fighting head on. |True power comes from the strength of one’s convictions. It would behoove you to not underestimate my abilities!
399030.feeling5: *yawn*.... I am getting a bit sleepy... and the Commander probably won’t ignore that... Indeed, the Commander would probably carry me back to bed... My intuition is seldom wrong... Hehe...
399030.upgrade: Even after gaining power, I, Kitakaze, shall keep a clear head.
399030.unlock: Indeed, the preparations are complete... Now that I, Kitakaze, shall be assisting you with your operational command, you can now sleep more soundly at night, Commander. Heheh!
399030.feeling4: I’m not... good with the dark. I, Kitakaze, shall slowly follow behind you!
399030.feeling1: Commander, if you continue to squander your talents, then one day...
399030.propose: My mind is at peace whenever I am by your side, Commander... so can I always keep you company? Can we pinky swear on it then? My sisters told me... that this is enough to form a vow with a person of integrity.
399030.skill: My single strike shall seal your fate!
399030.profile: Lead ship of the Super Akizuki-class... That is I, Kitakaze. During the war, I was not able to display my prowess upon the battlefield, but it is not too late to do so here. Bear witness to my agility as well as the strengths of my armaments.
399030.touch2: Hmm... The responsibility of cleaning up your conduct weighs heavily upon me, but... please cease your crass behavior.
399030.mission: Shape up, Commander. You can’t afford to just leave these missions sitting there.
399030.home: Good work, Commander. Please leave the rest of the work to me. I shall not disappoint you.
399030.win_mvp: A single victory is nothing to be proud of. Let us prepare for the next battle.
399030.expedition: The commission fleet must have returned with a lot of goodies. Commander, you should take a look.
399030.mail: Let’s check the mail. I have a feeling that something good has happened...!
399030.feeling3: My sisters always give me lots of candy whenever they see me. I, I suppose I can share them with you, Commander...

499060.detail: Yes, resist me. I look forward to seeing your reaction when you realize that all your struggling has been for naught.
499060.touch: What do you seek to learn from the Unhulde?
499060.login: Quiet, you... Your arrival has merely made my aide a little wary. Pay it no mind.
499060.hp_warning: tis too soon to start mourning for me.
499060.feeling2: To indulge in the sweet sap of sloth, or to swallow the bitter medicine of hard work? The choice is yours alone to make, Commander.
499060.mission_complete: "Mission" complete. Congratulations. Another small step towards that alluring, dangerous climax.
499060.main: What does being my familiar entail? You shall learn in due time.|You're awfully quiet... Have you given up already? Obedience does not amuse me.|I can read you like an open book when you stare at me, Commander.
499060.feeling5: People cannot say no to their hearts. Much like I cannot refute my love for you, you cannot deny your feelings for me. That is the link that binds us together.
499060.unlock: You've finally come, my familiar... Pardon, my "commander." I am the Unhulde, August von Parseval. 'tis a pleasure to meet you.
499060.feeling4: I enshackled you precisely so you'd want to rebel and make me submit to you. Why, you ask? Because I've been drawn to you all along. Now show me that fearsome potential that sleeps within you.
499060.feeling1: I have nothing to say to those who cannot fight.
499060.propose: So you seized the chance to subjugate me first. Yes, you are at your brightest when you kick and scream in the cage known as love. Allow yourself to be bound to me and amuse me for all eternity... Darling.
499060.profile: tis I, August von Parseval, Iron Blood aircraft carrier. I am but a vessel, but I am also the chains that bind you. Remember this, my familiar. Or should I say, "Commander?"
499060.touch2: You let your urges take control of you... Fine. Revel in the bliss of your inevitable, pathetic defeat.
499060.mission: I can't imagine you'll falter in the face of such simple trials. Or "missions," as you call them.
499060.home: I bid you welcome back, Commander. Well fought. I await the day you work up the courage to challenge me.
499060.win_mvp: I've achieved the victory you desired. It wasn't so hard.
499060.expedition: Your commission team underlings have returned. You know what to do now, yes?
couple_encourage: You seem like you'd know a thing or two about magic.
Your strength is worthy of admiration.
Show me the face of the Finale.
499060.mail: There's a letter for you. I command you to read it at once.
499060.feeling3: Zeppelin and I both know what you are. An insignificant insect, triying to defy your destiny. Having said that... I believe a soul like you isn't meant to blindly accept their destiny.
499060.lose: For every victor, there must also be a loser...

601060.detail: This course is a no-go because there's no resupply point along it? Okay, then how about this one? ...Also a no-go; ocean currents are too strong? Stop being such a darn naysayer, Commander!
601060.touch: Will you check out the course I plotted after I finish this work? Sweet! I'll have it done in no time!
601060.login: Ahoy! Good to see you again, Commander! Let's have a look at today's cruising plans!
601060.feeling2: Ahoy, Commander! Today's a perfect day to go on a voyage! First, we just have to plot a course!
601060.headtouch: Ow! Don't pull on my hairband!
601060.mission_complete: Mission complete! Can we go on a voyage now? What do you mean?! I thought we had a deal!
601060.main: Commander, got any maps lying around? I'm not gonna mess with them, I just wanna draw some lines, plot a few courses, that sorta stuff!|Hey, could I have a look at your medal collection? I'm just curious which and how many you have!|Why does everyone just take the same exact route over and over? There's so, so much ocean to see out there!
601060.feeling5: We've got a date coming up, you and I! Since I am the veteran navigator here, I'll do the course plotting... I mean, itinerary planning! ...You wanna do that yourself? Hmm... All right, I'll leave it to you!
601060.unlock: The port's newest arrival, that's-a me! Fun-sized navigator Nicoloso da Recco salutes you, Commander! Andiamo, towards uncharted waters!
601060.feeling4: "If you help me out enough, I'll consider taking that route"? Whoa, you mean it?! Sign me up as your assistant!
601060.feeling1: I'm going on a voyage! Without you! Buh-bye!
601060.propose: What's it mean to "link our hearts"? Will I know where you are when I'm out at sea, without even using a compass? Ahaha! If only it were so easy, am I right?
601060.profile: I'm a navigator, and let me tell you, I'm phenomenal! I fought hard alongside lots of my friends, and even made it through the war in one piece. My run-in with Force Q though, that was just blind luck!
601060.touch2: I may be short, but I'm stacked! Bada bing!
601060.mission: Get those missions done, on the double! I'll be stuck idling in port forever otherwise!
601060.home: Let's see, where should I plot a course to next...
601060.win_mvp: That's that annoying bunch dealt with! Now we can explore in peace!
601060.expedition: A commission's been completed! What do you say we try a different course for the next one?
couple_encourage: Eep! You again...
Andiamo, to uncharted waters!
601060.mail: New mail's come in! Maybe it's got info on the latest course developments?
601060.feeling3: By Neptune's name! Look, Commander, there's an uncharted area on our map! Who knows what secrets it holds! We should go there on our next voyage!
601060.lose: Err, what? Did I take us on the wrong course?

399031.drop_descrip: All the preparations are now complete... Commander, let us sally forth and conquer these festival grounds! ...But before that, can we get something to eat first?

213042.detail: Carrot juice has just the perfect consistency. You can put anything you like in the glass, and nobody'll know!
213042.touch: Bottoms up, like adults do! Drink up, Mark I!
213042.login: ello there! How about a glass of delicious and nutritious carrot juice? ...Wait, stop, not that one! THIS one's for you! Phew... Disaster averted...
213042.main: Shaking the bottle? Pfft, that's the oldest trick in the book. I'll teach you a newer one, Commander!|Oh bollocks! It's Nelson! Quick, Commander, I need a place to hide!|You're silly, Erebus. All I asked for was a little inspiration, not the full recipe for some kind of magic potion!
213042.unlock: Now for a ghost pepper while nobody's looking... Tee hee! Perfect! I wonder who'll be the lucky one to sip– C-Commander?! You didn't see anything suspicious... Right? Tee hee~
213042.drop_descrip: Now for a ghost pepper while nobody's looking... Tee hee! Perfect! I wonder who'll be the lucky one to sip– C-Commander?! You didn't see anything suspicious... Right? Tee hee~
213042.home: Bring our customers their drinks, Manjuus! And be careful so you don't drop them!

101060.detail: Ahh~ Commander! D-don't get so close all of a sudden!
101060.touch: Commander, I can feel your encouragement. I'll work even harder!
101060.login: Leave today's halftime cheering to me, Commander!
101060.battle: C'mon, everyone~ Let's fight with all we've got today~☆!
101060.feeling2: Cheering, outside of work? I don't... quite understand what you mean...
101060.mission_complete: I've got your rewards, Commander. Surely they must include some sort of surprise?
101060.main: Even if it's time to rest, we've got to keep fighting and dancing. Never give up!|Northampton thinks she can take me down? Hmph!|Fight~ Come on~ Eagle Union~ ☆!
101060.feeling5: You. Can. Do. It. Co-man-der! L! O! V! E! Co-man-der! L! O! V! E! Did my cheers of love reach your heart?
101060.upgrade: Now I'll be able to cheer on everyone even harder!
101060.unlock: Second ship of the Gridley-class, Craven, reporting in. Leave the halftime cheering to me!
101060.feeling4: If you ever want me to, Commander, I-I would love to come and cheer you on any time...
101060.feeling1: I'll go cheer someone else on instead. I might not be coming back today!
101060.propose: Commander, now we need to make a cheerleading team just for you. Hm? Of course I'll be the coach! Nobody else has feelings for you like I do!
101060.drop_descrip: Gridley-class destroyer - Craven, Hull Number DD-382!
101060.profile: I'm Craven, second ship of the Gridley-class, at your command. As a high speed torpedo destroyer, I was active in the Pacific theater with my little sisters, mainly tasked with night battle support.
101060.touch2: E-even if you're just trying to encourage me, there's... there's this thing called being too passionate!
101060.mission: We've still got unfinished missions, Commander!
101060.home: Perfect! We've earned a flawless curtain call today!
101060.win_mvp: Huh, I was just cheering everyone on... Oh well, this works too~
101060.expedition: No matter where they go, I'll always be my sisters' chealeader! C'mon, Commander! Lets go and greet them!
101060.mail: You've got new mail! Any inspirational messages to share?
101060.feeling3: You don't look very energetic, Commander. Should I pat you on the head to cheer you up?
101060.lose: Oh no... My cheering must not have worked...

501041.detail: Commander, did you know? The Dragon Empery has an ancient legend about the monster known as the "Nian." During the Spring Festival, every household will hang up couplets and set off firecrackers to ward it off.
501041.touch: I made this outfit myself. My sisters all said it looks good, ehehe...
501041.login: Fu Shun gets really excited around the Spring Festival, and will even drag Chang Chun and me around...
501041.main: F-Fu Shun, it... it's dangerous to take apart firecrackers like that... Eh? You're doing an experiment? |This year's couplet... Um, Commander, can you help me brainstorm ideas? |Chang Chun, it's a once-in-a-year occasion, it's not good to stay inside your room all day...
501041.feeling5: During the Spring Festival, relatives will all gather to celebrate a reunion. Th-this year, I'd like to have a reunion with my sisters and you, Commander... is that okay?
501041.unlock: O-on behalf of the An Shan class, we wish a prosperous, happy, and healthy new year to Commander, and to everyone here at port... Umm... even though I made this outfit, I feel a bit embarrassed wearing it... Eh? It looks good on me? Um... th-thank you...
501041.drop_descrip: O-on behalf of the An Shan class, we wish a prosperous, happy, and healthy new year to Commander, and to everyone here at port... Umm... even though I made this outfit, I feel a bit embarrassed wearing it... Eh? It looks good on me? Um... th-thank you...
501041.touch2: C-commander... if you keep messing around, someone's going to get mad!
501041.home: Ah, Commander, welcome back... I'm making a lantern... Would you mind helping me hang it up?

900161.detail: Don't be blinded by statistics. Victory depends on far more!
900161.touch: Body contact...? I don't hate it...
900161.login: As long as I'm here, we can deal with any enemy, no matter how far they are.
900161.battle: I would never let the commander's enemies escape!
900161.hp_warning: So this is how harsh the battlefield can be.
900161.feeling2: Commander, want to hear about the history of the Royal Navy? Maybe I should tell you something about the generals who used to accompany me.
900161.mission_complete: Missions give out rewards once you complete them. Don't forget that!
900161.main: Your orders are absolute, Commander. They shall be my highest priority.|This grand old lady can run faster without a skirt. Want to race with me?|If you make fun of me one more time, you'll be eating my 15 inch shells!
900161.feeling5: Well, enough of that. I'm Warspite, the one who spites war. Hmph! However, whosoever tries to take the Commander away from me will first have to face my cannons!
900161.unlock: Greetings, I'm Warspite. I hold the record for the longest ranged hit on a moving target. Surprised? I'm smaller than you thought? Looks like we need to have a long talk...
900161.feeling4: How do I put this... I'm considered to be one of the older girls, yet my body is like this... It might be unbecoming of one my age to compete with the younger girls, but I wanted to at least be attractive to you… What is a lady meant to do…
900161.feeling1: Would you please not act like we're close...
900161.propose: Finally the day has come! It looks like my efforts were not in vain... Let's go, Commander, I'm prepared for this. Officers, draw swords!
900161.drop_descrip: Queen Elizabeth-class battleship - Warspite, Hull Number 03!
900161.profile: Elizabeth-class fast battleship, Warspite, reporting in. I hold the record for the longest ranged hit on a moving target. I've come close to being defeated quite a few times, but I managed to cheat death every time. This must be my fate.
900161.touch2: Just so you understand, I'm definitely not that sort of, erm...
900161.mission: Accept your new mission and then get ready to head out, Commander!
900161.home: Whew, not a bad fight. Let's rest for a while.
900161.win_mvp: Don't be confined by the so-called "limits". It is indeed possible to be unsinkable!
900161.expedition: Commissions? I suppose I do miss running around on errands... Let's go. We need to welcome back those hard workers!
couple_encourage: Do you want to race this old lady?
Unmatched by any? *Sigh*...
Elegance does not belong on the battlefield.
Your Majesty, please look forward to my performance in battle.
Youngsters, follow me.
900161.feeling3: I'm not very elegant? I'm sorry that I'm not like Hood or the others... No... I'm not talking about my body...
900161.lose: My damage control isn't functioning?! I've lost control of my steering wheel as well! Why now, at such a critical moment?!

102123.detail: "Special Christmas lingerie"... I never should've listened to Louis! I need to put on this whole costume quick, before someone sees me...!
102123.touch: My plans for Christmas? Um, let's see... Hey, hold on, why are you asking that with a straight face to someone who's dressed like this?!
102123.login: C-Commander! You did that on purpose, didn't you?!
102123.main: *Sigh*... Just thinking about that idiot standing behind me with a straight face makes all my motivation go away...|I-I tripped just a moment ago, and these ribbons got all tangled up around me... Ahahaha, I'm such a klutz... What are the ribbons for...? U-uhh...|That's a wonderful Christmas tree...? T-thanks... Hey, hold on, don't you have anything else to say?!
102123.feeling5: *Sigh*... "Go visit the Commander and say 'I'm your present~!'"... That's ridiculous, the Commander would never like this stupid costu... D-did you just hear that?!
102123.unlock: Stupid Louis... "If you dress up as a reindeer for Christmas, you'll have an easier time talking to Helena"... You think I'm stupid enough to believe someth...? *Eeeeeek*?! C-Commander?! Get out, right now!
102123.drop_descrip: Stupid Louis... "If you dress up as a reindeer for Christmas, you'll have an easy time talking to Helena"... You think I'm stupid enough to believe that...?! *Eeeeeek*?! C-Commander?! Get out, right now!
102123.touch2: *Eek*?! Commander, when did you get here...?!
102123.home: Commander?! You sure chose an awfully convenient time to come back!
102123.mail: Your mail? Oh no... I forgot which box I put it in...
102123.lose: They're staring at me... They're staring at me...!

101130.detail: Don't forget to keep your gear in working order, Commander!
101130.touch: Aren't I so soft and squishy?
101130.battle: Sssh, be quiet! We need to coordinate with our sisters preparing to flank the enemy.
101130.feeling2: Want to take a walk together, Commander?
101130.mission_complete: Reporting in! Mission rewards have been delivered!
101130.main: Commander, won't you take Aulick out to play~?|Aulick loves hanging out with all the other Little Beavers!|Ah, Aulick likes the Commander too, of course!
101130.upgrade: I hope it'll come in use to you, Commander...
101130.unlock: Yaaay! It's so great to meet you, Commander! Just call me Aulick! ... What was that? I said Aulick! My name is Aulick!
101130.feeling4: Like a cookie - twist, lick, and dunk. D-do you want to give it a try, Commander?
101130.feeling1: You think it's funny to call me by the wrong name?
101130.propose: My Little Beaver sisters are for sure going to envy me now.
101130.drop_descrip: Fletcher-class destroyer - Aulick, Hull Number DD-569!
101130.skill: It's Aulick, I'm telling you! A-u-lick!
101130.profile: I'm Aulick of the Little Beavers! I was mainly tasked with air rescues. I'm not as strong as the captain, but I'll be more than satisfied as long as you let me fight till the end!
101130.mission: Commander, you've still got unfinished missions! You're being lazy, aren't you?
101130.home: This place is great, Commander~ I've grown to like it more and more!
101130.win_mvp: I'd never let you down, Commander!
101130.expedition: The girls are back from their adventure!
101130.feeling3: ... After being called sweet for so long, I think I'm starting to get used to it. ... You call me sweet because that's what girls are? I-is that a compliment?
101130.lose: Why does everything have to hit me in the face?!

501040.detail: Fu Shun just asked me to tell her about the Philadelphia Experiment. Commander, would you like me to tell you about it too?
501040.touch: Commander, what kind of books do you like to read?
501040.login: H-hey, Commander. I was too absorbed in reading that I lost track of the time...
501040.battle: L-live combat... I have to do my best...
501040.hp_warning: Eh...? U-um... what should I do...
501040.feeling2: Comm... Commander? Um, sorry, Chang Chun needs me for something right now!
501040.mission_complete: D-does this mean I've matured a little?
501040.main: F-Frank Knox? I don't want to run into her again... |An Shan is so hardworking... When can I be of help to her? |What am I reading right now? "Miscellaneous Morsels from Youyang." Chang Chun gave it to me...
501040.feeling5: Commander... even though I'm immature, I will work harder. So, um... please wait for me... Y-you'll be waiting for me to surpass my sisters? Th-thank you!
501040.upgrade: U-um... it's still a bit scary...
501040.unlock: I... I'm Tai Yuan, a destroyer. Commander, have you seen my sisters?
501040.feeling4: Commander, are you in here? Eh? I'm not just walking around.. Um, I just got a little lonely... and wanted to see your face...
501040.feeling1: An Shan, I... I'm a bit scared...
501040.propose: Thanks, Commander... Even though I'm still not very reliable, from now on, you can count on me!
501040.drop_descrip: An Shan-class destroyer No. 4 - Tai Yuan (104)
501040.skill: Let the heavens focus our minds, so we can adapt to any situation!
501040.profile: Um... I'm Tai Yuan, fourth ship of the An Shan-class and a first-generation member of the Dragon Empery's "Four Unbreakables." I originally was named "Ji Lin." My sisters and I were the mainstay of the Empery's navy for decades, serving in many operations and helping rebuild the strength of the navy. The "Nuclear Physics Hypothesis" is a very interesting book... It would be nice if my sisters liked it too...
501040.touch2: W-w-woah... C-commander, please don't do that...
501040.mission: This mission... looks quite difficult. Will we be able to do it?
501040.home: I can finally settle down. W-wait... Fu Shun, where are you dragging me off to?
501040.expedition: Eek! Someone came back... Oh, An Shan, I'm fine...
couple_encourage: To help An Shan, I have to do my best...
Fu Shun, you're charging up too fas- Ahh!
501040.mail: C-commander, there's new mail. Perhaps Fu Shun should... um, never mind...
501040.feeling3: Commander, other than my sisters, you're my first friend. S-so, um, whatever you do, please do not get inside Fu Shun's home-made missile!
501040.lose: Um... as expected, I still have a long way to go...

101262.detail: Commander...won't you be joining Eldridge for class?
101262.login: Commander, want to listen to music...with Eldridge?
101262.main: Not being by the Commander’s side while at school, interesting... |Everyone at school gets charmed by Eldridge’s cute gaze...Eldridge is elated! |nil
101262.unlock: Commander, do you like Eldridge...this way? Meow~...look what I've done to my books...
101262.drop_descrip: Commander, do you like Eldridge...this way? Meow~...look what I've done to my books...

103240.detail: One sec, gotta finish this message... There we go! You see, I offer this like, counseling service thing, so sometimes I get people messaging me like this. You need any counseling, Commander? Typing all the time's a chore, so just hit me up in-person.
103240.touch: Oof... My shoulders are killing me! Yo, Commander, mind giving me a massage?
103240.login: Nice seeing ya, Commander! I'll list off today's mission objectives... but first, I've gotta make a post to my Juustagram!
103240.hp_warning: I mighta been a bit too careless...
103240.feeling2: Welcome to Bremerton's counseling corner! So, whatcha got on your mind? ...Hang on, what? You just wanna chat? So... you want counseling on how to find a chat buddy, basically?
103240.mission_complete: Mission's been completed. We haven't claimed the rewards yet, though. Come on, head out and get 'em!
103240.main: You look kinda moody... Wait, is that my cue to like, go buy you a drink?|What are you like when you're not working, Commander? Maybe you're one of those serious-on-the-outside, klutz-on-the-inside people?|Is my outfit tickling your fancy, Commander? Heheh, if you wanna get a closer look, go ahead.
103240.feeling5: Did you read my DM, Commander? Don't go ghosting me; it says you've seen it~ I'm waiting for your reply with, like... Butterflies in my stomach, I guess? You know how to write a good reply, don't you? Hehehe~
103240.upgrade: Hooray! It feels like I've grown in some way! Or somewhere, but I dunno where that'd be...
103240.unlock: Here! I! Am! I'm Bremerton, the Eagle Union heavy cruiser! The pleasure's mine! Oh, by the way, mind telling me your name, birthday, and favorite thing?
103240.feeling4: I know you're used to listening to everyone else's troubles, but you can talk to me about whatever's on your mind. Oh, if you wanna talk through text instead, you can always DM me over Juustagram.
103240.feeling1: Come back to your normal self already, Commander... If you really need it, you can cry into my chest and let it all out.
103240.propose: Okay, now keep your eyes closed, Commander. "Why"? Come on, I'm not gonna mess with you, so just relax and do it~ I wanna remember this feeling every morning I wake up for the rest of my life♪
103240.drop_descrip: Baltimore-class heavy cruiser – Bremerton, Hull Number CA-130.
103240.profile: We Baltimore-class girls, me included, hardly got any chances to shine in combat since we were built near the end of the war. This time 'round, though, we're always on standby! You need somethin' done, hit me up!
103240.touch2: Do that again and you'll regret it real bad, you hear?
103240.mission: Are these missions tough stuff? Hmm... Maybe I'll take a look, see if there's anything I can help with.
103240.home: Phew... Hey, Commander, you're thinking about skippin' work, aren't you? Hah, I'm fine with that. It'll just be you and me taking a short break, nobody'll notice.
103240.win_mvp: Heheh! Lookit or not, I'm a Baltimore-class, so these chumps were easy-peasy!
103240.expedition: That commission team's come back! This is your chance to charm 'em, Commander!
couple_encourage: You ready to kick some butt, Baltimore?
103240.mail: Got a letter for you here. If it's nothing important, I could read it for ya.
103240.feeling3: Things I like besides fighting? I chat people up all the time and give counseling over social media, sooo... I guess I like hanging out with people? Oh, hang on, gotta check this Juustagram message. One sec...
103240.lose: Oops... Uhh, I think I messed up somewhere...

107072.detail: Cheese sure is good stuff~ By the way, Commander, do you like Sardegna-style pizza or Eagle Union-style pizza better? ...Me? It's all good to me, hahaha!
107072.login: If you can't decide what to order, get a bit of everything! Just kiddin'~♪
107072.battle: You're gonna regret looking down on Hornet big time!
107072.main: Want something to drink? Cola? Or maybe some oolong tea? What'll it be?|Hey, Hammann, don't just waste food like that! I, I'll help you out! ...Commander, I'm gonna need another stomach over here!|That Zuikaku, only ordering boneless wings... Eh? Bring the green chili sauce? ...Ah! Not a bad idea...!
107072.unlock: Mmmmm... Nothing beats pizza straight outta the oven! Here, Commander, wanna give it a try? We're gonna have to recommend this to Enty next time!
107072.drop_descrip: Mmmmm... Nothing beats pizza straight outta the oven! Here, Commander, wanna give it a try? We're gonna have to recommend this to Enty next time!
107072.home: Here, have some cola! I helped myself to a few bottles from Georgia's stash~ She's got plenty, she won't even notice they're gone!
107072.expedition: I also ordered some for the girls who'll be coming back from their commission. I'll swing by the dorms later, so you help out as well, Commander!

401019.detail: Heheh~ The mighty Z1 can get even stronger and faster!
401019.touch: Commander, I can't have you being this listless! Allow the great Z1 to pump you up!
401019.login: You're finally here! Come on, I want to start brawling already!
401019.main: Even my work productivity has doubled! Commander, can you even keep up with me~? |Viersechs, if you want a name, let me choose a great one for you: "Iron Blood Warrior Princess, Ritter der Walküre!" ...H-huh? You don't like it?! |Commander, do you feel like you can't get anything done without me? Ahahaha~!
401019.unlock: Hmm... So this is a retrofit, huh? Not bad! Rejoice once more, Commander, for no task or enemy is too daunting for the new and improved Z1!
401019.drop_descrip: Hmm... So this is a retrofit, huh? Not bad! Rejoice once more, Commander, for no task or enemy is too daunting for the new and improved Z1!

601050.detail: Now that I'm here, Maestrale's gonna make a whole lotta friends! ...Oh, right, Commander! Are you getting along with my sis?
601050.touch: Hey, what's the matter? Did something happen~?
601050.login: Ciao! Commander, let's give it our all today as well!
601050.feeling2: I wish I could get Maestrale some more friends! Commander, got any ideas?
601050.headtouch: Hold your horsies, Commander! Lemme take my hat off first... Now, pat me!
601050.mission_complete: The mission rewards huh... I may or may not have helped myself to a little when Maestrale wasn't looking... Ehehe~
601050.main: Maestrale's super good at organizing documents, isn't she? When I try to do it, they just end up messier and messier~|My hair's silver on the outside and blue on the inside! Beautiful, isn't it?|Commander, look over here! Kapow! Whew, a direct hit~! Ahaha!
601050.feeling5: Commander! I'm here to play again! I don't care what you're doing! I'm gonna cling to you today no matter what! Heh~ heh~!
601050.upgrade: Such powerrrr! Time to show off to Maestrale!
601050.unlock: Ciao! The name's Libeccio! It's a pleasure to meet you, Commander! Let's be real good friends from here on out!
601050.feeling4: Ehhh... Spend more time with me, Commander! What do I even want to do...? I don't care! Anything!
601050.feeling1: Knock knock! Yeah, I'm gonna keep thwacking you around until you behave!
601050.propose: What a beautiful ring! If I put this on, it means that I'll be able to cling to you as much as I want, right? It's a promise!
601050.skill: Let's have some fun over here~!
601050.profile: During that war, I was the pride and joy of the Sardegna Empire, Libeccio! ...Eh, I was the first of my sisters to retire? Booo! Commander, why do you have to rub salt in the wound!
601050.touch2: Smooth and flat, huh? Just like my big sis!
601050.mission: It's mission time! All I have to do is check off the box next to 'em, right... Of course that was a joke!
601050.home: Commander, look! Lookie lookie at what I found! It's the teabags that my sis always uses to make you tea! I wanna try it too!
601050.win_mvp: The MVP is all mine! Commander, gimme a reward!
601050.expedition: Commission complete! Duuuuude, look at the loot!
couple_encourage: Sis, follow my lead!
601050.feeling3: Commander, I'm here to play! You're not busy right now, right? Ehehe, after all, Maestrale made this... silly-bus for me? In any case, it seems right!
601050.lose: Starting emergency rescue procedures! Commander, make sure you keep me safe!

401020.detail: Commander, I have a question, do you have a thing for making others dress up in fancy clothes?
401020.touch: Oh, absolutely, I agree wholeheartedly. Now, what's our next task?
401020.login: Commander, I have a question: why do you always arrive later than me?
401020.battle: Be wary of ambushes and try not to overextend yourselves.
401020.hp_warning: My magazine is flooding... which is quite bad.
401020.feeling2: Is there anything you wish to know about Lebe, Commander? Oh, you're more interested in me? You're quite the curious one. Please give me a minute to think.
401020.mission_complete: I'll obey if you order me to claim the mission rewards, but my opinion of you will worsen. Is that an acceptable tradeoff to you?
401020.main: Commander, please try not to be as reckless as Lebe. It would be annoying to have to knock you out, and I don't particularly like getting physical with a superior officer.|I'll bring you a fresh batch of paperwork if you have nothing better to do. I hope you're ready.|This little one is Lebe. Yes, you heard that correctly; this is Lebe. Isn't she cute?
401020.feeling5: Commander, if you wish to take our relationship to the next level, simply keep being yourself; say what you want to, and do what you want to. That is all I need from you.
401020.upgrade: Won't I develop some sort of flaw if I get even stronger?
401020.unlock: I am Z2, Georg Thiele, awaiting your orders. However, if your orders are flawed, please allow me to reconsider them. May our relationship be productive.
401020.feeling4: You are a commander with many strange ideas, but that may just be the perfect fit for a person with Lebe for an arm like me.
401020.feeling1: I don't mind being near you, but I'm afraid that Lebe does.
401020.propose: So this is marriage. I never thought I'd form an unbreakable bond with someone... What was that? I'm blushing? Umm... could you please take a photo of me right now? I've never seen myself red in the face before.
401020.skill: I can still go faster. Just a bit more.
401020.profile: I am Georg Thiele, otherwise known as Z2, a Type 1934 destroyer built as an experiment. I was to make quick work of adversaries using my excellent mobility, or at least that was the plan... I'd rather not elaborate. Please forget I said that.
401020.touch2: Among all actions that take bravery, this would, in my honest opinion, be the worst kind.
401020.mission: We've received new missions. I organized them to give you a solid overview. You're welcome.
401020.home: I've put together an after-action report, as you ordered. Please have a look.
401020.win_mvp: There are countless examples of seizing defeat from the jaws of victory. Let us not underestimate our foes.
401020.expedition: The commission team has returned. Naturally, we should greet and praise them for their hard work. I can accompany you, if need be.
couple_encourage: Please don't take it too far, Lebe. The cleanup would be annoying.
Ride the waves and sail the... Never mind I said anything.
401020.mail: You have mail. I propose that you open and read it as soon as possible. You are prone to forgetting about it, otherwise.
401020.feeling3: You want to make small talk again? Why? You should know that the only answers I ever offer are nods and affirmations. Could it be that you actually like canned responses like that?
401020.lose: I'll cover everyone. I'm quite good at these things, owing to Lebe's help. You may rest easy.

601051.detail: How the heck do you make a sand castle? Like this? Or maybe... like this...? Gaaaah! I give up!
601051.touch: Get on, Commander! We're going on a field trip!
601051.login: One, two three, four... All righty, I'm all done warming up! Time to head down into the water~!
601051.headtouch: Yes, pat me to your heart's content!
601051.main: Sailor Libeccio, ready to head out! Captain da Recco, when do we begin the timber-shivering?|How can I get Maestrale to join us in the fun and games? ...Hmm, take some beautiful conch shells over to her?|Commander, look at that! So many footprints in the sand along the beach... Huuuh?! Th-they got washed away just like that...
601051.unlock: Libeccio's heading towards the sea! Commander, let's go to where all the excitement is!
601051.drop_descrip: Libeccio's heading towards the sea! Commander, let's go to where all the excitement is!
601051.touch2: Commander, what kind of game is this~?
601051.home: Glub... Blub...! Blehhh, it's so salty... My kickboard flipped over in the blink of an eye... I guess I really shouldn't head out until the waves calm down a little!

101061.touch: These courses are too hard...Commander, can you tutor me?
101061.main: When you are overwhelmed by all this learning, go for a jog to relax yourself!|If you're struggling with the material, then find a tutor. If that doesn't work, get special training...nothing can’t be solved through special training!|The Commander has always been the best in my heart, so I have to be in his heart, too!
101061.unlock: I much rather cheer for my Commander than go to class...but no matter where I go, I will definitely give it my all! Commander, wait for me to come back as the top student of this school year.
101061.drop_descrip: I much rather cheer for my Commander than go to class...but no matter where I go, I will definitely give it my all! Commander, wait for me to come back as the top student of this school year.

499050.detail: My serpents have a tendency for violence, so be aware of the risk should you dare to touch me, Commander.
499050.touch: Would you like it... if I came a bit closer?
499050.login: Who might it be that just stepped through those doors? ...Oh, it's you. Best of luck with your work, then.
499050.battle: I shall tear you asunder! Ahahahaha!
499050.hp_warning: Caught on to me, have you...
499050.feeling2: My interests in life? Hahaha! Fighting worthy foes, savoring good beer, gazing at the stormy seas, and... What? Are you grasping at straws just to get my attention?
499050.mission_complete: Mission complete. I suppose you are at least qualified for your position.
499050.main: Insufficiently motivated, are we? A dinner with copious amounts of beer can fix that.|You like gazing at seas in tempest too, do you? Hahaha. A sea is at its truest when a storm rages through it.|...What? You have that look on your face like I'm distracting you.
499050.feeling5: You're in over your head if you thought you could drink one named after the god of the sea under the table. What's the matter? Can't move a muscle? Then I've proven my– Eek!
499050.upgrade: Prosit. The occasion warrants a toast. Mmh!
499050.unlock: Well met. I am large cruiser Ägir. Your will is my command. Hehehe... Now let's find out what you can accomplish with my arsenal of talents.
499050.feeling4: I don't mind your efforts to win my interest, but must you stare holes through me? Hehe. I suppose you're more daring when drunk... W-wait, you aren't drunk?!
499050.feeling1: You are undisciplined trash not worthy of my compassion.
499050.propose: A symbol of our marriage? You must adore having proof of the ties that bind you to me. Prepare to double down, then. I'll find something that binds you to me. Physically... Hahaha! You shall see what I mean.
499050.skill: Ahahahahaha! Be engulfed by my maelstrom!
499050.profile: I am Ägir, named after the very same mythological ruler of the sea. Though, compared to a god who smote adversaries with storms and crashing waves, my way of dealing with my enemies is much more subdued. Ahahaha.
499050.touch2: You're brave, I'll give you that... What?! Twice in a row?!
499050.mission: I see we still have unfinished missions. Do them now, and I shall refrain from dismissing you as incapable.
499050.home: You wish to rest, do you? I'm afraid the heap of soon-due paperwork on your desk won't allow it.
499050.win_mvp: Those fools were but splashes of water beneath my bow. Hahaha... Ahahahahaha!
499050.expedition: A commission has been completed. How long must your subordinates wait for you to acknowledge them, hmm?
couple_encourage: If you would, do mind your manners.
We shall drink later, but now, we must fight.
499050.mail: A letter has arrived from afar. Read it, would you?
499050.feeling3: I'm going for a drink, and you shall accompany me, Commander. Get as drunk as you wish. I'll overlook whatever silly things you say while under the influence.
499050.lose: Nobody, and I mean NOBODY denies me my victory! I shall return with a vengeance!

401022.drop_descrip: Being able to see you all flabbergasted makes changing into this outfit worth it. Are you going to keep standing there like a scarecrow? Come over here~ Who knows, we might even be able to see the fireworks from this spot.

207090.detail: Illustrious is steady in her steps!
207090.touch: Commander's hand is so big... much bigger than mine...
207090.login: Good day, Commander. I helped organize a little bit based upon how you had things before. How does everything look?
207090.battle: Bad guys that disturb the peace will be dealt with, like this!
207090.hp_warning: For the sake of love and peace, I must not be scared!
207090.feeling2: Commander, for the sake of love and peace, you mustn't quarrel with others, all right?
207090.mission_complete: Mission complete! Thanks to your efforts, we'll be able to further spread the light of love and peace!
207090.main: My planes? They're right here. Ehehe, everyone's so well-behaved. |Commander, I'll be there for you any time you're feeling lonely.|What an even more wonderful world it would be if everyone could understand each other.
207090.feeling5: Commander, you seem to not be feeling well... Are you tired from working too much? Hm... Ah, Commander, here... *pat pat* What a sweet child~ I heard this will help you not be tired... right? Ehehe, don't you feel better already?
207090.upgrade: With this, I'll be able to further spread the light of love and peace...
207090.unlock: Good day to you, Commander. I am Illustrious of the Royal Navy. We'll spread the holy light of love and peace all across the ocean, right~♪
207090.feeling4: I heard that sitting down to talk with someone can help relieve your worries. Commander, if there's anything bothering you, I'd be glad to hear you out.
207090.feeling1: Were my prayers for love and peace not even enough to reach the person closest by my side...?
207090.propose: S-so this is a promise ring... such an important thing, for me...? Ehehe, thank you so much! I may still be immature, but I will work hard to become the person of your dreams. No, I'm sure I'll be able to do it~♪
207090.drop_descrip: Illustrious-class aircraft carrier – Illustrious, Hull Number 87.
207090.skill: Holy light, pummel our enemies in the name of love and peace!
207090.profile: I am the world's first armoured aircraft carrier, ehehe. One day, I'll do my best for the glory of the Royal Navy!
207090.touch2: Is this some sort of new game...?
207090.mission: Commander, are you worried about the unfinished missions? Is there anything I can help you with?
207090.home: Good job, Commander. Would you like Illustrious to give you a back massage?
207090.win_mvp: We're one step closer to a world of love and peace.
207090.expedition: Everyone has come back from their commission. I'll have to hurry to bring the refreshments out to them!
couple_encourage: We'll mess them up in the name of love and peace! Understood!
If you're bored, why don't we play a game...?
Miss Sara, could you teach me a song?
Let us bring love and peace to this battlefield!
207090.mail: Commander, there's mail for you. Umm, where did I put it... Oh, there it is! Here!
207090.feeling3: Ah, Commander, wait a second... Here, use my handkerchief... Ehehe, there are some cake crumbs stuck on the corner of your mouth~
207090.lose: For the sake of a world of love and peace, next time... you won't get away!

101263.detail: These clothes, pretty. But hard to hug. Sad...
101263.main: Commander, hair bun, big... Want to touch it?|Commander, glasses, cute?|Commander, cherry flower. Watch. (Eldridge's lock of hair is taking the form of a cherry flower petal.)
101263.feeling5: Commander, hold hand. With you, go together to... (Eldridge's lock of hair is forming a heart.)
101263.unlock: Commander, Sakura Empire's New Year looks fun... Go together...? (Eldridge is looking at you expectantly.)
101263.drop_descrip: Commander, Sakura Empire's New Year looks fun... Go together...? (Eldridge is looking at you expectantly.)

202233.detail: So I need to put this headband on... I wonder what kind of hairstyle would be good? Um, let's tie my hair up like this... Actually, maybe twintails would be better instead?
202233.touch: Um... This outfit really is quite embarrassing...
202233.login: Commander, what will your first order be?
202233.battle: Take a deep breath, Swiftsure... Everyone, please commence attack on the enemy!
202233.main: Commander, is something wrong? ...Is this outfit really too stimulating, like Sheffield said it was...? Or... is it actually too conservative, like Fiji said it was...?|Everyone acts much more freely when they're at the beach. Do you think I should do the same? A-Alright, I'll give it a try... Y-Yo!|When I'm helping Neptune, I feel like a completely different person. ...Oh. What would you like to have, Commander?
202233.unlock: W-welcome! ...Ugh, I'm still way too nervous... Ah, um! H-how may I serve you today, Commander...?
202233.drop_descrip: W-welcome! ...Ugh, I'm still way too nervous... Ah, um! H-how may I serve you today, Commander...?
202233.home: Welcome back, Commander. If... If you'd like, please enjoy this refreshing beverage...
202233.mail: Commander, there's new mail for you. I apologize, but I didn't have the time to check its contents beforehand. If it's alright with you, I'd like to check the contents with you, right now...!

103241.detail: Gah, it's freakin' hot... I just wanna hit the showers and then flop around in bed until it's time to sleep... Oh, gotta update my Juustagram... Ehh, forget it, I'm not gonna bother today.
103241.touch: Now that I'm all sweaty and gross, I can't just ask to lean on your shoulder, can I? Ahaha...
103241.login: *gulp* *gulp* Phew... I'm coming back to life! Coach, thanks for practicing with me all this time!
103241.main: Coach, if you're thirsty, you can take a sip from my water bottle. Don't sweat the small stuff, go for it! |Seems like Cooper is having a match with some Sakura Empire girls over on the next court. Coach, wanna go take some sports drinks over to them in a bit? |Wanna have a friendly match? Er, actually, scrap that. There's no way I'd be able to beat you, Coach.
103241.unlock: *pant*... *pant*... Man, it's so sunny today... Commander, or should I say, "Coach," could ya lend me your parasol? I'm starting to feel my brains melting away...
103241.drop_descrip: *pant*... *pant*... Man, it's so sunny today... Commander, or should I say, "Coach," could ya lend me your parasol? I'm starting to feel my brains melting away...
103241.touch2: I was an idiot for thinkin' you wouldn't try something when my guard is down...
103241.home: *pant* *pant*...Unlike Baltimore, I guess I'm really not built for this kind of exercise...
103241.expedition: That commission team's come back! This is your chance to charm 'em, Coach!
103241.mail: Got a letter for you, Coach. If it's nothing important, I could read it for ya.

501031.detail: Fu Shun said she's planning to blast apart an underwater volcano to turn the entire ocean into a hot spring... Thankfully, I don't think the water is getting any warmer~
501031.touch: Tai Yuan has recently taken a liking to resting against me while reading. Commander, would you like to try it as well?
501031.login: A day's plan starts in the morning, a year's plan starts in the spring, and a life's plan with diligence. Commander, make sure to work hard, okay? I'll be cheering you on quietly from my dreams~
501031.main: Commander, An Shan and Fu Shun are making dumplings tonight. What kind of filling would you like? |Commander, let me massage your shoulders~ |Fu Shun, do you still not have enough firecrackers? How would I know if this is enough to boil the entire sea?
501031.unlock: Ta-da! My pajamas are finally finished! Now to snuggle up until I'm all warm! Eh~ Ehhh? But sis, I don't want to get out! Ack, did Tai Yuan purposely make this tail big and thick to make it easier for you?
501031.drop_descrip: Ta-da! My pajamas are finally finished! Now to snuggle up until I'm all warm! Eh~ Ehhh? But sis, I don't want to get out! Ack, did Tai Yuan purposely make this tail big and thick to make it easier for you?

301249.detail: Being able to come to this port, and now even receiving a retrofit... Looks like my luck's not too bad, hehe~
301249.touch: Interested in my tail? Well, I guess I'll let you touch it. You'd better be grateful~
301249.main: Hatsuharu doesn't seem to be as scared of strangers anymore. Heh, looks like you've been taking good care of her~ |Hmm, what are you staring at? Naughty Commander~ |*staaaare*... Oh, I'm just carrying out my secretary duties of observing you, Commander~ Don't let your mind wander so easily~
301249.unlock: Hatsushimo's retrofitting is complete. You don't think I look all that different? Oh, Commander, you're still as simple as ever~ I've changed in tons of ways beyond what's just on the surface. Heheheh~
301249.drop_descrip: Hatsushimo's retrofitting is complete. You don't think I look all that different? Oh, Commander, you're still as simple as ever~ I've changed in tons of ways beyond what's just on the surface. Heheheh~
301249.touch2: Do you want to experience for yourself... the less visible parts of me that have changed? Commander~?
301249.home: Good job~ But... there's still a lot of work left to do. Hehe, do your best~

900243.detail: I've inspected the communication equipment. It won't cause any more problems...
900243.login: Commander, have you eaten yet? Here's some snacks.
900243.hp_warning: I don't want... to be alone...
900243.feeling2: Ayanami's impressions of Commander? I don't really know.
900243.headtouch: I don't really get it but... I'm a bit happy...
900243.mission_complete: The rewards for the previous mission are here.
900243.feeling5: I don't particularly... like or dislike combat. I just do what must be done. But if it's for you, Commander... maybe I can get a bit stronger.
900243.unlock: I'm... Ayanami. I am often called the "Demon." Pleasure to meet you.
900243.feeling4: If there's one thing that worries me... it would be when you are not at my side.
900243.feeling1: I don't really want to get any closer.
900243.propose: Rest assured... This time, no matter what happens, I'll survive and return to you... because I'll always want to see you again...
900243.drop_descrip: First ship of special Type II {namecode:6} class destroyers, {namecode:6}.
900243.skill: Bear witness to the true power of the "Demon"
900243.profile: I am Ayanami, an improved Fubuki-class destroyer. I am not afraid of combat. Though just a destroyer, I can fight any enemy...
900243.touch2: Commander... please... don't touch there so much... It's making me feel weird...
900243.mission: Commander, we've been notified of new missions.
900243.home: Commander, you're a little like me on the battlefield... That's... pretty cool.
900243.win_mvp: MVP? I don't really get it, but... thanks.
900243.feeling3: Commander, you're always saying that my ears are cute... But why won't you touch them?

301490.detail: I like fishing. When fishing, you can just clear your mind and not think about anything.
301490.touch: How I feel about secretary work? Work is work, I don't have any preferences. Secretary or not, I don't care.
301490.hp_warning: This pain... isn't enough to distract me!
301490.feeling2: In war, there is no right or wrong, no beauty or ugliness. This is true for both ally and enemy.
301490.mission_complete: Mission rewards are here. Let's see if they were worth the time. But first, accept them.
301490.main: Shells are weapons to silence one's enemies with. That's all they are, no matter how you sugarcoat it.|If there's something you're wondering, ask Jintsuu. I'm... if I must say, I'd say I'm more like Sendai.|Pretty cheerful gang you've got going with this fleet...
301490.feeling5: "Your dreams will come true if you don't give up on them"... Hmph, what a trite answer. But, if that's what you say...
301490.unlock: The name's Kawakaze of the Shiratsuyu class. I have no intention of becoming your friend. Spare me your introduction.
301490.feeling4: I abhor the stupidity and naïveté of those who refuse to face reality and continue shouting about their hopes and dreams. But you're not like that... are you?
301490.feeling1: In the end, you're just someone who can't exceed my expectations, Commander.
301490.propose: I'm astonished that I'm doing this with you... We've been together so long that your wishful thinking has rubbed off on me... And for doing so, you'll take responsibility, won't you...?
301490.skill: Relax. I will end this in an instant.
301490.profile: I'm Kawakaze, 3rd ship of the improved Shiratsuyu class, or simply the Umikaze class. Destroyer Division 24 comprised of my sisters and me during the war. Ah, Solomon... True, it is a place of many memories. The Iron Bottom Sound, Northampton, and the last thing I remember...
301490.mission: New mission's appeared. ... What? Do I have to make small talk with you?
301490.home: What happens when the battle ends? The next one begins, that's all.
301490.win_mvp: The Solomon Islands... they call for me...
301490.expedition: A commission's done. Don't forget to read the report.
couple_encourage: And now, we're allies? ... Fine.
Lady Nagato, please be careful.
Let us work with each other's strengths!
301490.mail: Mail for you. Me? Not a fan of the stuff...
301490.feeling3: Have you not experienced war, too? Then why do you still believe in fairy tales like justice, love, or harmony...?
301490.lose: I'm still... afloat. If that's good or bad, who can say...

501030.detail: I definitely am not hiding the stuff that Fu Shun secretly bought.
501030.touch: Commander, if you like this outfit, I'll ask Tai Yuan to make a set for you as well.
501030.login: Good morning, Commander~ Ehehe, looks like it's not even morning anymore though~
501030.battle: Why must we... fight each other?
501030.feeling2: I heard that Prince Rupert's drops can be used to ward off the evil monsters that come out at night, so I told Fu Shun. The windows at the academy are gone? I-I have no idea what you're talking about~
501030.mission_complete: Next up is... Ehh? What's that burning smell coming from the warehouse? Ah, my snack...
501030.main: The four of us are authentic noblewomen, you know~ |During the summer, Tai Yuan will make a breezier version for me, so there's no problem. |Fu Shun, I heard that terrifying monsters appear in the academy after the sun goes down.
501030.feeling5: You want me to take off my cosplay? Ehehe~ I suppose I can, but you'll have to do what I say!
501030.unlock: Destroyer Chang Chun has arrived~ No, I'm not afraid of the cold~ I just like being warm and cozy~
501030.feeling4: Commander, the beach behind the academy is perfect for swimming. Uh, I wasn't making plans or anything! I was just playing around with my binoculars when I saw the swim ring that Commander had bought, ehehe~
501030.propose: If you never leave my side, I can consider your request~ Just kidding! Your gullibility is a good thing though~
501030.drop_descrip: An Shan-class destroyer No. 3 - Chang Chun (103)
501030.skill: Let the seven heavenly mansions align for the coming of the white tiger!
501030.profile: I am Chang Chun, the third ship of the Dragon Empery's An Shan-class destroyers, and one of the "Four Unbreakables." As one of the pillars of the Empery's navy, I played a pivotal role in the training of personnel. Eh? Fu Shun is getting into trouble again? An Shan is going to be worried...
501030.touch2: Commander, is this the type of person that you are?
501030.home: I'll help give everyone a massage! Pain, pain, fly away~
501030.win_mvp: Clear skies and calm waters today as well~
501030.expedition: Commisson complete! Looks like someone has snacks for me!
couple_encourage: Understood, I'll intercept the enemy with everything I have!
Don't just flail around, if you get scared, just hide behind your big sis!
501030.mail: New mail, huh? Seems like the perfect thickness to stick under this wobbly table.
501030.feeling3: Hey Commander, how'd you get in here? Secret base? Ehehe~ I have no idea what you're talking about~ Oh, by the way, have you seen my snacks? W-wait, you can't eat that!
501030.lose: Wow, I think I goofed up~

301242.detail: Commander, please be mindful of the girls who tend to get lonely easily. Like Kasumi, for example... Hmm? She's perfectly fine? ...Was I misunderstanding something?
301242.touch: Though I don't quite stack up compared to Wakaba and Naganami, I've got plenty of confidence when it comes to the size~ of my tail, of course. Heehee~
301242.mission_complete: You know that you still haven't picked up the rewards, right?
301242.main: I see, I see. So this is one of Ikazuchi's "creative dishes!" ...I have no freakin' clue what this is! Hey, Salt Lake City, how about you?|I wonder what that stuff is that the Northern Parliament girls are always drinking... Feels like something I shouldn't look too deeply into.|Russian Roulette with candy? Hmm, count me in. I don't lose at this kind of stuff.
301242.unlock: Cheers, Commander~ C'mere, you've got to enjoy the party too! If you're thinking of doing something tactless like running off to go back to work, people are going to get upset with you~
301242.drop_descrip: Cheers, Commander~ C'mere, you've got to enjoy the party too! If you're thinking of doing something tactless like running off to go back to work, people are going to get upset with you~
301242.mission: Yeah, yeah~ Still have unfinished work~? Nothing wrong with saving it for another day~
301242.home: Good work, everyone~ You've also been working hard today, Commander. Accept my gratitude and be thankful! Hehe~

900242.detail: If you have the time to stare at me, shouldn’t you go back to your studies? Even I... can get embarrassed...
900242.touch: If you’re free, why not help with some paperwork?
900242.login: There's still quite a lot to be done today. No procrastinating!
900242.battle: Let’s go! It’s time to reap the rewards of our hard work!
900242.hp_warning: I've got to find a way out of this mess...
900242.feeling2: Studying is important! A wise man once said, "knowledge is power." ... France is bacon? Jeez... just what is going through that head of yours?
900242.headtouch: I’m not the kind of girl who you can fool with just a few headpats. Get back to work, Commander.
900242.mission_complete: Commander, the mission rewards have arrived.
900242.feeling5: Commander, did you know that the higher you stand, the further you can see, but also the lonelier you will be? I hope that you can rise to great heights one day, but still be as happy then as you are now.
900242.upgrade: Commander, I hope that we'll improve, together!
900242.unlock:
Guten Tag, Commander.
I am Z23. Let’s study hard together and aim for the top!
900242.feeling4: Commander, why are you staring at me? You think I’m pretty when I look serious? I-idiot! Go do your own work...
900242.feeling1: Commander, can you not bother me when I’m trying to study?
900242.propose: This is the proof that Commander acknowledges me... Understood. From now on, I shall stay by your side and work hard to ensure that your life is happy and upstanding.
900242.touch2: This isn’t something a commander should be doing...
900242.mission: Completing missions is a great way to hone your skills. Don't ever forget that!
900242.home: We still have so much to review about the previous battle...
900242.win_mvp: Battles are like exams. Earning MVP is like getting the top score on a test.
900242.expedition: It’s about time! Please put aside your work, and check on the results of your commissions.
couple_encourage: Z25, let's do our best together!
900242.mail: There’s mail for you, Commander. You sure are popular.
900242.feeling3: You’re a bit tired? Very well, getting rest is important. You want a lap pillow? I guess it’s fine... just for a little while...

900245.detail: If gods truly exist in this world, let us begin our slaughter with them.
900245.login: The black goat's horn has already sounded. Quell your anxiety and wait at ease.
900245.battle: Let us begin our symphony of destruction.
900245.hp_warning: The smell of steel and blood...
900245.feeling2: Ahh, so sweet. Sweet things cannot last for long. The only thing that endures forever is ice-cold hatred.
900245.feeling5: As long as you are here, the world does not feel so insipid and detestable. Rest easy; even if the world was to become your enemy, I would happily fight by your side. As a matter of fact, I eagerly await this day.
900245.upgrade: Ah, if only strength alone was enough to determine everything.
900245.unlock: You're my Commander? I am Graf Zeppelin. Since it appears that all the conditions have been met, let the final movement begin.
900245.feeling4: I have never been one to believe in fate, but if meeting you was also predestined... Hmm... How ironic. For the gods to have given me the worst past but also the best future... what purpose does my hatred then serve?
900245.propose: Oh? Have you finally decided to make the entire world your enemy? What? You just want to be with me? Hmph, very well. Eradicating everything that stands in our way doesn't sound bad either.
900245.profile: I am Graf Zeppelin. Though this name is worth little, you may call me by it if you wish. My only desire? To end the world. I shall not ask for your help though... as you are already a part of my plans.
900245.touch2: Quite brave, aren't you? As expected of the one I chose.
900245.mission: Is the person who gave you this mission really who you want to fight for?
900245.home: All your fights, all your struggles, are nothing more than fodder for the End.
900245.win_mvp: My enemies belong in their graves.
900245.expedition: Ah, so they have returned... Just seeing those faces filled with joy...
900245.mail: Treasure the time you have to speak with your loved ones, for that time is about to draw to an end.
900245.feeling3: Does prayer really work? Will God ever respond? Nein. Gods are called as such because they are merciless.
900245.lose: Next time, I shall grant you despair even worse than death.

301491.touch: Do you like kendo, too? I'll work you to the bone to make you good at it. ... Huh? You don't wanna do it?
301491.login: Today might actually be an eventful day.
301491.main: On the battlefield, you swing your weapon and defeat the enemy, no more. Thinking about other things comes after the battle.|Sendai, how about we have a match? As for our spectators... I suppose we could ask Jintsuu and the Commander.|Seems having some cheerful people by your side might not be so bad.
301491.unlock: Mhm. Lightweight clothing makes it easier to fight. Thanks, Commander... "It looks cute on me"? W-well, thanks...
301491.drop_descrip: Mhm. Lightweight clothing makes it easier to fight. Thanks, Commander... "It looks cute on me"? W-well, thanks...
301491.touch2: Phew... I was considering chopping off your hand, had you gone any further.

202110.detail: I'm not going to give these to you no matter how much you stare at me.
202110.touch: Hey!! Don't touch that! It's gonna fall!
202110.login: Ah! I'm not doing anything weird! I'm just transporting gold bars into the room!
202110.battle: Wh-Wh-What to do?? First let's retre... I mean, intercept them!
202110.hp_warning: Gh... At least let me protect the gold...!
202110.feeling2: Everything goes well when 'that girl' does it, so it should be fine if I'm a little clumsy, shouldn't it?
202110.headtouch: Thanks! I'm feeling a bit more energized.
202110.mission_complete: I seem to have forgotten about something... Well, whatever!
202110.main: I want to be as elegant as Hood but, well...|Eeeh! ...Bel, where are you? I forgot my keys again...|Hmhmm~ Even Scharnhorst had to turn tail and run away when she saw me!
202110.feeling5: Commander, want to have a walk together before it gets dark? Yes, don't worry. The lights were switched off, and the windows were shut. Everything's OK! ... W-what? ...Wh-Where did the keys go?!
202110.upgrade: It seems like I've become luckier!
202110.unlock: This is my turn, you might say! I am 'her' older sister, Edinburgh! In a sense, I am the 'most accomplished' light cruiser!
202110.feeling4: Phew... I've finally found you, Commander. Actually... Aaaah-- Who the heck! Who left the banana peel here!
202110.feeling1: Since it's Commander, I have to be even more careful... *stare*...
202110.propose: Hmhm, I'm fine with sharing some of my money-luck with you. ...The gold? No! That belongs to the Belfast Foundation!
202110.drop_descrip: Edinburgh-Class light cruiser ー Edinburgh, Hull number 16!
202110.skill: No matter how thick the armor is, it can't win against the power of gold!
202110.profile: I am the lead ship of Edinburgh class of the Royal Navy. Sometimes it is stressful having an overly capable little sister... I took part in the pursuit of Bismarck and Scharnhorst, as well as many patrol missions in Atlantic, North sea and Mediterranean. In the end, I sunk with all my gold due to Ironblood torpedoes...
202110.touch2: Commander, a lady would never hide her gold bars there!
202110.mission: You have to finish your missions properly!
202110.home: I made cookies! Please have a taste... They taste the same as Bel's? Well, we're sisters, after all!
202110.win_mvp: Crushing the enemies with elegance... That, is the elegant Ediburgh of the royal family!
202110.expedition: When it comes to military commissions, I'm a pro!
couple_encourage: I didn't think I'd get a chance to fight with Belfast!
Sheffy, I'm counting on you!
Newcastle, let's talk about Bel sometime!
Echo, dear, do take care!
202110.mail: Commander, there's a new ma... Wh-What? Where's the mail? Where did I leave it... ??
202110.feeling3: I've been lectured by Bel again... Forgetting to lock doors when going out, and turning off the tap... What the heck! She's totally not like a little sister!

900244.login: Once you get used to waiting, you lose sight of what you were waiting for.
900244.battle: Commander, I shall fight for your sake.
900244.hp_warning: No one would protect those who asked for their own destruction.
900244.feeling2: I have already grown used to the cold solitude of the North. At this point, it's natural for me to have no expectations.
900244.feeling5: Ahh... I see. I thought I was used to the cold and embraced it, but that was just because I had forgotten the joy of human interaction and the warmth of being with someone... But now I remember...
900244.upgrade: If you have no opponents, all the might in the world is meaningless.
900244.unlock: I was imprisoned in the north for so long, unable to return home, and now you want me to follow you? ...Very well. It is up to you to show me the world.
900244.feeling4: The worst feeling in the world is not knowing whether to continue waiting or to give up hope. Commander, are you someone worth waiting for?
900244.feeling1: In the end... are you just another incompetent fool, unable to command me?
900244.propose: Ahh... so this is the warmth of one's beating heart... It's melting the cold and despair remaining within me. Danke sehr, Commander. The "Queen of the North" is no longer alone.
900244.touch2: I'll think of how to deal with you later.
900244.mission: Finish your missions properly. Perhaps you will one day realize the joy of having any purpose at all.
900244.home: Commander, you should show your face on the battlefield more often. If you stay behind your desk for too long, you may one day forget the meaning of life.
900244.win_mvp: So this... is the taste of victory.
900244.expedition: The commission seems to be complete... Next time, why don't you let me go? I'm a little curious.
900244.mail: More mail for you... Ah, I'm envious.
900244.feeling3: Those who have nothing to lose also have nothing to fear... But is this kind of bravery really anything to be proud of?
900244.lose: So this is... the frustration that comes from failure and fear.

103040.detail: Don't just stare at boring numbers all day... how about staring at something with more meat to it for a change?
103040.touch: I'll show you how to have a good time~
103040.login: Don't get too into ignoring me, okay, Commander~?
103040.feeling2: The night is still young, Commander. Why don't we have some adult fun together? ... Just kidding~!
103040.mission_complete: Our rewards are here. You're always out there pulling off great stunts, aren't you, Commander?
103040.main: Women can change as quickly as the wind in Chicago, Commander~|At this distance, nobody else can hear us~|Your shoulders are so stiff. How about a massage to help you relax?
103040.feeling5: Oh dear, you don't look too good. Too much pent-up stress, perhaps? ... Then let me do the cooking. I have some responsibility of you too, after all~!
103040.upgrade: People are counting on me, so I'll need to work hard too~
103040.unlock: So you're the commander? You're looking at me almost like you want me to feel you up. Things will get fun starting tomorrow.
103040.feeling4: I've been a little more moderate lately? Indeed. That's because, for the first time in my life, I've met someone dear to me. That's why I need to behave myself~
103040.feeling1: You still have a lot to learn about women, Commander...
103040.propose: I've restrained myself for so long waiting for you to give me this. But now that I have it, there's no need for self-restraint, is there? That being the case... you should brace yourself, Commander. Cause you won't be getting away from me~
103040.drop_descrip: Northampton-class Heavy Cruiser – Chicago, Hull Number CA-29!
103040.skill: Oh my, you're not getting away from me!
103040.profile: I'm Chicago, fourth ship of the Northampton-class. I've never really done anything noteworthy in battle, and I've never been particularly lucky. But I'll do my best for you, Commander. So be nice to me~ *Kiss*
103040.touch2: Aahh~ You're a naughty boy, Commander~
103040.mission: I put your new missions in order... Even I can actually do my job sometimes.
103040.home: Well done out there. Come here and use my body to recover your energy~
103040.win_mvp: I'm expecting some juicy rewards when we get back~
103040.expedition: Looks like the girls who went out on a commission have returned. How about we do something fun before we go greet them?
103040.mail: You've got new mail, but it seems to be stuck here... Come~ take~ it~!
103040.feeling3: Most people aren't very good at dealing with me. You have a peculiar taste in women, Commander...
103040.lose: Oh no, my clothes are torn~!

399040.detail: I need more experience if I'm to keep up with the others... So please give me something to do. Hehehe.
399040.touch: Oh? You want to touch me? Or would you like me to touch you? You'll have to come out and say it.
399040.login: Shall we begin the day's work? Do not worry, I will be right here with you the whole time.
399040.battle: I am to lead the fleet...? I shall not make any promises, but... I will do what I can!
399040.hp_warning: A little wound like this, it's nothing...!
399040.feeling2: I still have trouble finding my way around... Pardon me, Commander, do you think you could find time to accompany me on my patrols...?
399040.mission_complete: So many mission rewards... Commander, you're fantastic.
399040.main: This defense power will definitely be useful in battle!|My guns are very precise...? Thank you for saying so. I think it's more the result of training than any natural talent. Hehehe.|Commander, is there something you would like from me?
399040.feeling5: Commander, are you tired? Hehehe. Then come here and lie down. Let Azuma clean your ears... Hmm, after a shoulder massage, I think.
399040.unlock: Large cruiser, Azuma, reporting for duty. As a special prototype ship, there are many things that I am still unfamiliar with... However, I will lay down my life to protect you, Commander. It would please me greatly if you would place your trust in me. Hehe~
399040.feeling4: You know what, Commander? The most delightful thing in the world is a happy smile... All the smiles, and of course your smile, Commander, I will protect them all.
399040.feeling1: Commander, I'm worried about you... You can do better, can't you?
399040.propose: Now that I understand your feelings, Commander, I will offer you all that I am, body and soul... Phew... Saying that out loud is as embarrassing as I thought it would be. Hehehe.
399040.profile: I am Large Cruiser Azuma. I was designed to lead torpedo squadrons into night battles, but I never saw any actual combat. I'm quite good at commanding night battles, but torpedoes are another story... Ahahaha...
399040.touch2: Commander? There's a time and a place...
399040.mission: Is it a very difficult mission? I can help.
399040.home: Welcome home. Commander, I have tea, snacks... and a massage chair here for you. Why not take a load off?
399040.win_mvp: This was the result of everyone's hard work. I was merely part of the team.
399040.expedition: The girls you sent out on commission have returned. Would you like me to inspect the rewards for you? Commander?
couple_encourage: Miss Deutschland, if you wouldn't mind showing a bit of humility...
I still can't compare with you, Kongou.
Kitakaze, don't get lost now, okay?
399040.mail: I got the mail. Please look it over.
399040.feeling3: I'd like to get to know the other Sakura girls, and the others besides. What do you think of holding a mixer...? I could provide... the refreshments! Hehehe.
399040.lose: We lost... How will I tell the Commander...?

103110.detail: Relish in the power of a true heavy cruiser!
103110.touch: What is it, want to have a go with me?
103110.login: You've returned. You really kept me waiting. Get ready to depart.
103110.hp_warning: How about unveiling what secret plan you have in store for me?
103110.feeling2: My dream is to conquer the world! What happens after I've done that? Hmph, who cares about that!
103110.main: Torpedoes? Far too weak!|Look! Our conquest extends to the ends of this blue sea!|There exists no problem that a shot from my huge cannons cannot resolve!
103110.feeling5: Listen, Commander. I was just joking about it at first, but if we join forces, we might just be able to conquer the entire ocean! Since what's mine is yours, there won't be any need to split everything equally, am I right?
103110.unlock: You're the commander? Very well. Starting today you will be my adviser. You will devote your time to helping me conquer the seas!
103110.feeling4: Though it may be a little late, I really wanted to thank you for putting up with my selfishness and staying with me... Will you continue doing so? Hah! That's just that what I wanted to hear, Commander!
103110.feeling1: Hmph, it seems I made the wrong decision... by relying on someone as useless as you...
103110.propose: I see you as my best friend... No, I'm not planning on treating you as my best friend... Hold on, let me think for a moment. No, that doesn't mean I'm turning you down... Just give me some time to ready my heart for this...
103110.drop_descrip:
Wichita-class heavy cruiser – Wichita, Hull Number CA-45! 
<color=#ffde38>Unlock build after receiving</color>
103110.skill: This shot will be it for you!
103110.profile: I am the one and only fearless general of the seas, Lady Wichita! Even carriers would be crushed beneath my feet, if I wanted to end them myself. That's why, Commander, I'll be expecting much of you.
103110.touch2: Are you trying to get a taste of my whip?
103110.mission: A new mission? Read it out loud for me.
103110.home: Good work, Commander. You should rest as well.
103110.win_mvp: Hah! These weaklings are no match for me!
103110.expedition: Hm? Looks like a commission's been completed... Hmph, a few commissions are easy pickings for our mighty fleet.
couple_encourage: Ahahahahahaha! Show me what secret plans you have in store to satisfy me with!
Heavy cruisers, attack!
Kaede's Legion, follow me!
103110.mail: I'm entrusting the mail to you.
103110.feeling3: You're curious about my whip? Well, I bought it on a whim long ago, but it's been surprisingly useful. Particularly when I'm pointing at a map.
103110.lose: Now this is interesting. Hmph, fall back!

299010.detail: Want to know about this? It's called a trident. Don't you think it's cool?
299010.touch: You would like to challenge me to a game? Very well. Do not expect me to hold back though, hehe~♪
299010.login: That simply will not do, Commander, keeping me waiting all this time~
299010.battle: So this is a battlefield? Ahaha... how interesting.
299010.hp_warning: I seem to have underestimated the battlefield...
299010.feeling2: Commander, I have a question. If in the future you were given the option to sacrifice me for world peace, what would you choose?
299010.mission_complete: Commander, what do you hope to gain through not collecting the mission rewards? Perchance you are waiting for me to remind you?
299010.main: Unlike the other girls, this is my "maiden voyage" onto the battlefield. I wish to confirm for myself what this oft-touted "difference in experience" looks like. |Commander, if you get on your knees and beg, "Please, Mistress Neptune," perhaps there would be a chance for something nice to happen? |Commander, if you wish to taste my freshly-baked cake, then please first brew your finest tea~
299010.feeling5: Commander, have you planned where we're going to go for our date? If you have picked out an outfit for me, why don't you help me put it on? Eh~? "Why don't I wear it myself?" Silly, that's what love is all about~ L.O.V.E~♡
299010.unlock: Who am I? I am the Royal Navy's large light cruiser, Neptune. I shall see to it that you will never forget my name~♪ Yes, pleased to be of service~♪
