299010.feeling4: Having that said, I believe that a truly intelligent person knows how to rely on others when appropriate. Ah, that's right~ Commander, would you feed me some cake?
299010.feeling1: Commander, did you know how high my expectations were for you at first? What a shame, for you shall now never know.
299010.propose: "You are my world?" Did you think you could fool me with such flattery? Ehehe... well, I suppose there's a chance that I would let you fool me~ But first, you would have to repeat it ten times, nay, a hundred times~
299010.skill: I have no intention of getting friendly with the enemy~
299010.profile: My background? Ehehe, I am the large light cruiser who only existed on paper, Neptune, so it is understandable that you have never heard of me before. Though I have yet to step onto the battlefield, my abilities are top notch... allow me to prove that to you in live combat~
299010.touch2: That simply will not do, Commander. You cannot seek to gain my attention that way.
299010.mission: Commander, I see you have allowed your unfinished missions to pile up. I am not very fond of lazy people, you know?
299010.home: You've done well to return home safe and sound.
299010.win_mvp: Ehehe~ As a special service, I shall allow you to praise me more~♪
299010.expedition: Commander, I shall temporarily grant you permission to leave my side so that you may greet the girls who have returned from commissions.
couple_encourage: I-I wouldn't do something like that...
Let's seize a decisive victory, Miss Head Maid~♪
Let me see how the Maid Team fights~♪
299010.mail: Commander, there's mail for you. Hmm? I didn't do anything in particular~
299010.feeling3: The correct answer is - to do everything in your power to prevent that situation from occurring in the first place. Heehee~ Commander, if you wish to woo me, you will have to use your brain more~
299010.lose: I shall not repeat this mistake again.

900241.detail: Commander, you care so much about me... I'm so very happy!
900241.battle: This seems like a good way to kill time!
900241.hp_warning: Everyone, let's work hard! For the commander's sake!
900241.feeling2: ...I'm cute? ...Eeeeh~! You're lying, right? Commander, are you trying to trick me again~
900241.mission_complete: Commander, Commander! Let's go check out the rewards!
900241.main: Let's work hard for the whole day!|Fwa... I don't like to feel nonexistent. I'm gonna strike back~|I'm very lucky!|Commander, Commander, let's play with me~!|Commander... it feels safe by your side~
900241.feeling5: Being together with you makes me so happy, Commander~ Ah, I made a boxed meal. Do you want to try some?
900241.upgrade: Hehe, your care is very heart-warming, Commander!
900241.unlock: I'm Javelin, Commander. Nice to meet you. Oh ho? You look like you have no idea what to do with a girl of your type being assigned to you!
900241.feeling4: Commander, you see, I want to be confessed to under the legendary tree like in comics~ and stuff...
900241.feeling1: Commander, if you don't behave yourself, I am going to start disliking you. You hear me?
900241.propose: Commander, what's wrong? Your face looks frozen... Eh? ... Wait, my heart isn't ready... what to do, what to do, my hair is messy and I haven't put on any makup or a dress... Commander, wait for me! Definitely wait for me!
900241.drop_descrip: J-class destroyer ー Javelin, Hull Number F61!
900241.profile:
Good day, Commander! I'm the J class destroyer Javelin! 
My sisters and I were part of the Narvik battle and the evacuation of Dunkirk! I had a little trouble along the way, but I fought until the very end!
900241.touch2: Kyaa~! Commander, perverted behaviour is bad!
900241.mission: Commander, Commander, new missions have been issued!
900241.home: Great work, Commander. Do you want a back massage?
900241.win_mvp: Am I amazing? Oh you shouldn't have~ But, please learn how to do a better job praising me!
900241.expedition: Getting tired? The commissions should be done just around this time. Shall we go to the docks to welcome them back?
couple_encourage: Witness the power of the J-class!
Let's work hard for the Commander!
Kaede's Legion, fight!
900241.feeling3: I've gotten closer to you now, Commander. Hehehe. But I'm gonna have to work harder~
900241.lose: Ugh... I let my guard down...

103242.detail: Bremerton's counseling corner's still open, like always! Got somethin' you wanna talk about, Commander?
103242.touch: Ooh, that's good... Your muscles get real stiff after so much action.
103242.login: Hoo! Hi-yaaah! Whew... 'sup, Commander? Came to watch? Cool, cool. Never mind me though, check out this ballin' backdrop Akashi hooked me up with!
103242.battle: C'mon, show me what ya got!
103242.headtouch: I know hairbuns are cliché, but I wanted to change up my style, y'know?
103242.mission_complete: Mission donezo! Got another scene coming up, so we'd better go get those rewards now.
103242.main: Have you seen Ning and Ping's mad acrobatic skills? The stuff they can do legit blows my mind...|Hi-yaaah! Oh yeah, frickin' nailed it! 103242.unlock: "Stop right there, evildoers! You've managed to evade justice all this time, but the hour of judgment is finally upon you!" ...Hmm, making the perfect flashy debut is pretty tough, isn't it?
103242.drop_descrip: "Stop right there, evildoers! You've managed to evade justice all this time, but the hour of judgment is finally upon you!" ...Hmm, making the perfect flashy debut is pretty tough, isn't it?
103242.touch2: Heheh, you really wanna taste my kung-fu fury that badly?
103242.expedition: Commission team just got back. You know what that means: we gotta give 'em a true kung-fu hero welcome!

399041.detail: E-even if it's for a picture, holding this pose all this time is not easy...
399041.touch: Having you here, Commander, makes me feel at ease.
399041.login: Commander, the Spring Festival is a busy, exciting time. But do take care not to catch a cold when you're out having fun.
399041.main: I understand these "Tangyuan" soup balls have some association with "unity" or "gathering" in the language of the Dragon Empery, but if I eat the tangyuan, doesn't that mean I've broken the unity?|Our friends are drawing that "Fu" character everywhere, so I went ahead and tried my hand. I think I did alright... Ahahaha...|Do you need help with the decorations in your office? I'd like to give decorating a try.
399041.feeling5: Are you tired, Commander? Hehe, with all this carousing it's only natural that you'd get worn out. Now then, rest your head on Azuma's bosom for a while.

399041.drop_descrip: Commander? Oh, I haven't quite finished changing. My hair still needs work... Sorry, would you mind waiting a bit longer?
399041.touch2: Don't do that! At least, don't do it right now...!
399041.home: Commander, would you mind giving me a moment of your time? Only for a little bit. I'd just like to know what it feels like to monopolize you for a while... Hehehe, I'm only joking.

900235.detail: Buli? Buli? Where are we? What are we gonna do here?
900235.touch: Buli? Do you want to be bulified?
900235.login: If I swing this wrench hard enough, I could poke a hole in the office floor, buli!
900235.battle: I don't know what I'm doing, but I'm doing it, buli!
900235.feeling2: My big sis can apparently only strengthen one color. I can strengthen a bunch! Which means... that I'm more powerful than her? Wow! I'm stronger than her, buli!
900235.mission_complete: Rewards... Can I eat them, buli?
900235.main: Us Bulins are pretty awesome, buli!|Is there nothing for Bulin to do? Really? Then let's go play! Wheee!|Commander, let's go dig for some treasure, buli~!
900235.feeling5: My heart races whenever I see you, Commander! I could dismantle the entire dock for you! Could this be... my inner fire? Buli!
900235.unlock: Buli? Seems like I can help make your fleet stronger, buli!
900235.feeling4: I'm not meant for combat, yet you use me anyway, so being the more sensible Bulin, I need to thank you! I guess it's just because we're too cute...? *Kyah~* I might be in love~!
900235.feeling1: Wahh~! Commander is a big, big dummy!
900235.propose: Bulin has been caught~ Ahh, I'm blushing so much! What will I do! Let's buy some new toys and celebrate!
900235.drop_descrip: Universal Bulin. Can be used to limit break all ships of Elite rarity or below.
900235.skill: My wrench is the wrench that will pierce the earth!
900235.profile: They say I'm just like my sister, but we're actually in charge of different colors... What's a color? Sounds yummy!
900235.home: Buli! Look, I'm full of energy!
900235.win_mvp: Buli? Could it be that... I'm super strong?!
900235.mail: Something strange just popped outta me, buli...
900235.feeling3: Bulin is happy that she can help everyone get stronger, but she enjoys playing with you too, Commander! Bulin can help strengthen you... Aww, why not?

401280.detail: Commander, look at this torpedo! I drew a funny face on it! Cute, isn't it?
401280.touch: Please go to sleep already! You can wait until later to finish the work!
401280.login: Ah... Commander, I'm sure you had your reasons for being late! Anyway, it's fine, don't worry about it! Let's just word hard starting right now!
401280.hp_warning: A fearsome foe... Everyone, be careful!
401280.feeling2: I wonder what the little birdies are talking about from their tree branch up there... I've always wanted to know...
401280.headtouch: Ehehe, let me pat your head too~
401280.mission_complete: Another mission completed flawlessly! As a reward, I'll give you a hug~♪
401280.main: I want to play with cute animals all day long~|This big old office feels a bit empty, but it's also refreshing and helps me focus on work!|If you finish all your work on time, I'll make some delicious sweets for you~
401280.feeling5: Are you tired, Commander? Here, come put your head in my lap. Please lie down and have a pleasant dream, until all your fatigue and worries melt away one by one~
401280.upgrade: Mmm... if only they could make my rigging a little cuter as well...

401280.feeling4: Did you finish your work today? Mmhmm! As a reward, I'll give you a hug~♪ Good job, good job~
401280.feeling1: I'll continue to support you until you reflect on your behavior and regain everyone's trust. Don't give up!
401280.propose: I never thought I'd get something like this from you, Commander... I'm overjoyed! Please dote on me as much as you'd like from now on! No matter what, I'll always be there for you!
401280.profile: As a lead ship, I may not be as qualified as my sisters due to my armament... As a result, I've come to value problem-solving in other ways rather than directly fighting.
401280.touch2: All the girls will hate you if you do stuff like this, you know?
401280.mission: Looks like we have some new missions... Any tasks to go play with Meowfficers?
401280.home: Good work, Commander! Here's a hug for your safe return!
401280.win_mvp: We won! Commander, you're really awesome!
401280.expedition: Commission complete! Commander, if you're busy, I'll go welcome back the commission team!
couple_encourage: Sis, you're way too strict with Commander~
Z24, I have no idea what you're talking about...
Z25, shall we go take a look at Mr. Anchor?
Let's calm down and take things one step at a time!
Scharnhorst, you look so cool when you're out there fighting!
401280.mail: The little birdies brought me a letter~ Should I read it aloud for you?
401280.feeling3: Did you want to take it easy for a bit? Sure, I don't mind covering for you. But, there's no replacement for the work you do... so please take care of it later~
401280.lose: There's no need to feel down. Since we managed to retreat safely, there will always be a next time!

900258.touch: Your warm hands keep me energized to keep fighting, Commander!
900258.login: Ready for orders, Commander. I am confident in any kind of battle!
900258.battle: Is that it? Hah! Swordfish squadron, prepare for battle!
900258.hp_warning: If only a destroyer would give me a hug!
900258.feeling2: I... I'm going to say this in advance, but... those destroyer girls... u-um... I kid of... I mean... I kind of hold them dear... I know how to mind my manners... It's not... it's not a crime!
900258.mission_complete: Commander, to leave your rewards unclaimed is disrespect to the mission.
900258.feeling5: If I were closer to you, Commander, I could get closer with the destroyers too... Of... of course, that can only happen with your approval. I'm more than happy to help you with destroyer inspections! Is that all right, commander?
900258.upgrade: Oh! oh! oh! Allow me to protect you, my destroyer friends!
900258.unlock: Ark Royal, reporting in for duty! I am confident in all manners of battle. Why, it was I who managed to destroy Bismarck's rudder!
900258.feeling4: G-good grief... If you were the same size as those destroyers, Commander, I wouldn't be so embarrassed... I was fine with doing this with the little ones... but with you...
900258.feeling1: You can't compare with the destroyers, Commander...
900258.propose: I'll take care of all the destroyers from now on! No one can touch Commander or my destroyers. No one!
900258.drop_descrip: Aircraft carrier – Ark Royal, Hull Number 91!
900258.skill: It's time for you to leave!
900258.touch2: Eh... Commander... please don't... Why are you doing this?!
900258.mission: Commander, it's a soldier's duty to complete missions!
900258.home: Is it time for a break? I'm going to see my destroyer sisters then!
900258.win_mvp: An enemy who loses their ability to steer will be doomed!
900258.expedition: Commissions have been completed, Commander. If there are any cute destroyers in the fleet, allow me to welcome them back myself.
couple_encourage: I feel so strong now!
I've got to set an example for the others!
900258.mail: Do you need to me read out your mail, Commander?
900258.feeling3: I thought you were finally going to have me Court Martialed, Commander! I'm grateful to finally be recognized by you. It's nothing to be ashamed of? Commander, I, Ark Royal, will follow you forever!

102181.touch: Even though lollipops are a must-have, but apple candy also have a distinct apple flavor. Sigh… it’s so hard to choose~
102181.login: The night-time events at the Temple Fair is starting soon, shall we go take a look?
102181.main: Hmm… with my hair up like this, I can’t properly wear my headphones~ Commander, do you want to give it a try~? Perhaps it’ll be very suitable on you. |Hmm… walking around this temple is very tiring, hehe, can you give me a piggyback ride Commander?~ |On occasion, it’s nice to try out more exotic dresses. What do you think Commander, does this suit me?
102181.unlock: Apple candy, Taiyaki, and fried noodles~ The Sakura Empire’s Temple Fair really is something~ Hehe Commander, do you also want to take a bite of my apple candy? Here you go~
102181.drop_descrip: Apple candy, Taiyaki, and fried noodles~ The Sakura Empire’s Temple Fair really is something~ Hehe Commander, do you also want to take a bite of my apple candy? Here you go~
102181.touch2: Commander~? You can either be kicked or stepped on by me, please choose?

301251.detail: Parties are "a world of adult pleasures...?" Hmm, who's been putting weird ideas into Yuugure's head? ...Could it be you, Commander?
301251.touch: You want to be my dance partner? Ah, um! Sure, if you're fine with that.
301251.login: Commander, want a balloon? I have all kinds here!
301251.main: Yuugure, it's not every day we get to attend a party like this, so you should show off your stuff! Besides, you look super cute in your dress. Right? See~?|If we tied a balloon to Shiratsuyu, she wouldn't get lost easily, right? After all, we'd be able to see it from anywhere.|Who's been going around telling kids that you can fly if you tie a bunch of balloons together? ...Hatsushimo, can you stop giving them strange ideas?
301251.feeling5: As promised, I'll now be your doting little sister~ Mmhmm, take good care of me, Commander~
301251.unlock: Hope everyone enjoys the oodles of balloons I made for this party! Yeah, I'm sure the little girls will love 'em!
301251.drop_descrip: Hope everyone enjoys the oodles of balloons I made for this party! Yeah, I'm sure the little girls will love 'em!
301251.touch2: Woah?! Ah, Commander, you made my balloon fly off...
301251.home: Phew... Time for a little break...

102251.detail: A friend told me this look would totally steal your heart. So, has it? Are you head over heels for me? Hahahah! I'm just kidding with you.
102251.touch: Getting tired? Then let's catch a breather. Oh yeah, could you pour me some wine? Let's have a toast. To a wonderful day!
102251.login: Where do you wanna go today, Commander? Don't worry, we don't have to rush it. I've got plenty of time to spare.
102251.main: These Dragon Empery signs are really unique, in a good way. I think they're fascinating.|The seat on this Manjuu cart is pretty small. I'd offer to share if there was more room.|I was just about to go procure some souvenirs. What would you buy if you were me, Commander?
102251.feeling5: I came up with something that could make our trip more interesting. How about we give the Manjuu a break and *you* pull the cart to our next destination? Hahahah! I'm just joking around.
102251.unlock: We're celebrating an overseas holiday, hence my not-so-casual outfit today. Heheh, what do you think? Looking slick?
102251.drop_descrip: We're celebrating an overseas holiday, hence my not-so-casual outfit today. Heheh, what do you think? Looking slick?

106013.detail: It being Halloween and me being a ghost, I went around trying to scare people, but it was too much work so I gave up and just went back to NEET it up in my room instead.
106013.touch: Tired after all that work, Commander? Here, have one of my cushions~
106013.login: Commandeeeer! Come help out with my streaming setup~ Hehehe, come on~ I'll give you all the snacks you can eat in return~
106013.main: Hm? This message is from "Prancing_dragon_warrior," who says: "L.I., please impart more of your pro gamer knowledge to me!" Uhh, sure, I guess. We can do a viewer co-op stream later.|Someone's at the door? Commandeeeer! Grab some of the snacks by the bed and give them to whoever's knocking~|If I can make this streaming thing pay then I'll be able to buy new games without it killing my wallet! You should give it a try too, Commander~
106013.unlock: "Tune in everyone, Gamer Girl L.I. is about to begin her spooky Halloween special stream~" ...Well, that should do it for my channel intro... Hmm, wonder how many viewers I'll get~
106013.drop_descrip: "Tune in everyone, Gamer Girl L.I. is about to begin her spooky Halloween special stream~" ...Well, that should do it for my channel intro... Hmm, wonder how many viewers I'll get~
106013.home: It's easy to get burnt out when you do nothing but game streams... Oh, I know! Let's assemble a scale model instead next stream!
106013.lose: Oh no, my viewership is going down!

900255.detail: A flagship must lead from the vanguard. This is a self-evident truth.
900255.touch: Even the most hardworking people sometimes have lapses of judgment. It is my duty to admonish you in times like these.
900255.login: Until we've reclaimed our former glory, we must never stop pressing forward!
900255.battle: The fate of our country rests upon this battle!
900255.hp_warning: Keep calm! This battle is far from over!
900255.feeling2: Thinking about how I won't see old friends from back in my day ever again, it's... Well, never mind. I have people who look up to me now, and I can't let them down!
900255.mission_complete: Very well. I shall plunder... I mean, receive the spoils of victory!
900255.main: The victory at Tsushima did not occur by chance. |Royal cuisine? I'll pass... I've had enough of that. |Those things flying through the sky... Err, they're called "ear-playings," right?
900255.feeling5: You can't fire on all four boilers all the time. Listen, I'm going to look the other way while you take five... You've been wanting to nap on my lap? I-I guess that'd be okay...
900255.upgrade: Only the battlefield can separate the wheat from the chaff.
900255.unlock: I am the one who braved a hail of bullets and shells to return to my homeland with glory and victory. I am Mikasa, pre-dreadnought battleship of the Sakura Empire and flagship of the 1st Fleet, awaiting your command!
900255.feeling4: Yes, I can tell you've been working hard. B- but! That doesn't mean you get to start goldbricking now!
900255.propose: You still got a long way to go to earn my respect! ... Hehehe, so that's why I better stick by you? 'Til you're too good even for me.
900255.skill: Let every ship do her utmost!
900255.profile: I am Mikasa, a Shikishima-type battleship, and last of the Six-Six Fleet shipbuilding program. I served as the flagship of the Combined Fleet, and won a glorious victory that honored the name of our country across the world.
900255.touch2: You'd like me to be your dance partner at the next banquet? ... I-I suppose I have no choice...
900255.mission: Hmm, I'm in charge of today's fleet operations? Very well... the fate of our country rests... mmf! ... Why aren't you letting me speak?
900255.home: Excellent! The scales of war are tipping in our favor!
900255.win_mvp: Through righteousness comes prosperity. Such is the will of the heavens.
900255.expedition: Without robust logistics, even the mightiest fleets will turn into a disorderly mob.
couple_encourage: We fight together for humanity itself!
Steel yourself! And press the attack!
Never fear, the Sakura Empire is your ever steadfast ally.
Be careful. Misuse that power and we're worm food.
900255.mail: No matter how many medals and honors I receive... Ehehe~?
900255.feeling3: If you don't have a plan to end a war, then you'd better not start one to begin with!
900255.lose: So this what it must have felt like to suffer through the Battle of Dan-no-ura...

105020.detail: Huh? What are you looking at? Is there something on my face?
105020.touch: Commander, your hand feels comforting to me...
105020.login: Commander~ Please work hard with me today as well~
105020.battle: Everyone, listen to my orders and get into formation!
105020.feeling2: Is the Commander looking at me? Ehehe, I'm so happy!
105020.mission_complete: Don't forget to claim your rewards!
105020.main: If I don't do something soon, everyone will laugh about the 'Bantry Bay Squadron' again!|In two years... no, one year, I will surpass my sister for sure!|Commander, I will always listen to your troubles if you have any, you hear?
105020.feeling5: Hmm? Ah, Commander. No need to worry about me. I'll be happy as long as I can keep looking at you like this~
105020.upgrade: Commander, is there any way i can help you with this?
105020.unlock: Commander... eh, ah... I'm sorry! I was stunned just by looking at you... Ah, no, no... Nice to meet you! I'm Oklahoma!
105020.feeling4: Commander, I was smitten at first sight~ Ehehe. There's no particular reason for love. I just like what I like.
105020.feeling1: I wonder if my eyes are lying...
105020.propose: Ehehe~ Commander, let's go and report to big sis about us right now~
105020.drop_descrip: Nevada-class battleship – Oklahoma, Hull Number BB-37!
105020.profile: I'm Oklahoma of the Nevada class. I served in both the Atlantic and Pacific fleets... I even bore the duty of engaging in 'friendly' diplomacy!
105020.touch2: Whaa?! Geez... My heart wasn't ready for this...
105020.mission: Let's finish the missions like a speedy swifty!
105020.home: Commander, please tell big sis not to worry about me.
105020.win_mvp: With this, big sis won't have to worry about me! I think.
105020.expedition: The commissions have been completed. It would be nice if this brings peace.
105020.mail: I've put your mail on the table, Commander~
105020.feeling3: Commander, want to go on a date with me? I know a lot of good shops around~
105020.lose: *Cries*... I need to work even harder!

900254.detail: In both love and war, one should be brave~ So, be brave, and if you need support, I shall be there!
900254.touch: When you feel down, I also do. Come on, you have someone as beautiful as me beside you, so why not be happy?
900254.login: The quiet sea, the cool sea breeze... Even in this moment, the birth of new, beautiful things blesses us.
900254.battle: Sigh, all that cannons and gunpowder can do is make is war even uglier...
900254.hp_warning: Oh dear, I've let my guard down.
900254.feeling2: You know about me from the Battle of Trafalgar? Umm, aren't you thinking of somebody else? Please, Commander~ Who you're thinking of is totally unrelated to me.
900254.mission_complete: Fine, but just this one time! I won't help you with your missions a second time!
900254.main: War is ugly. And this olive wreath is the symbol of peace and beauty.|Tirpitz, if you won't come out and have fun with me then I'll bomb your room again!|I don't like violence, but using it is often the quickest solution to many problems...
900254.feeling5: I wonder what the future you will be like, Commander~ Of course, I already quite like the way you are right now. ...Goodness, you're blushing ear to ear. How utterly adorable you are~
900254.upgrade: Words are not needed to praise me! It's not people's words that touch the heart, it's their actions!
900254.unlock: I am the one called Victorious, Aircraft Carrier of the Royal Navy. Yes, sing my name as you herald the coming of the symbol of victory. As long as I am here, our endeavours shall be smooth!
900254.feeling4: I'm not in such a great mood... Are you free, Commander? Great! Then let me dress you in something fabulous! Seeing beautiful things makes me feel better, you see!
900254.feeling1: I'm fed up~! I'll knock you out stone cold!
900254.propose: Don't think too hard about it. Just follow my lead at your own pace. ...Come on, this is a day to celebrate, don't be so nervous~ From this day on, you'd better work hard to always please me!
900254.skill: O beautiful world, sing to me a song!
900254.profile: I'm Victorious, Illustrious-class aircraft carrier number two! From the Atlantic Ocean to the Indian Ocean, and even the Pacific... where the ocean breeze goes, I follow!
900254.touch2: Y-you just did "that," didn't you?! B-by "that," I mean...
900254.mission: Only I have the privilege of being selfish. Don't even think about pushing missions onto me.
900254.home: To celebrate your victory, why not wear this olive wreath? I'm certain it'll suit you.
900254.win_mvp: When my foes have been this thoroughly defeated... not even I, the symbol of victory, can truly be glad.
900254.expedition: Stop loafing around! I promised the commission team that I'd use my planes to photograph the moment they entered the port!
couple_encourage: Pleasure to meet again, little Ms. Flat-As-A-Pancake.
Illustrious, y-your bust is just too busty!
900254.mail: Handwritten letters are so much better than typed ones. Don't you think it's interesting how you can deduce the author's emotions based on their handwriting, Commander?
900254.feeling3: My part in the pursuit of Bismarck and Operation Tungsten? I was just in the mood to help, I wasn't at all trying to earn any honours.
900254.lose: Remaining dignified even in defeat: this is how one should lose a battle!

401251.detail: Mr. Anchor has to sit out in the sun as well, or he will get moldy.
401251.touch: I'm not tired yet, there's no need for you to massage- Ooh... that feels pretty good...
401251.login: Phew... It's been a long time since I've been able to enjoy such a refreshing breeze.
401251.main: Volleyball? Or how about swimming! I won't lose, no matter what you pick! |Liven up! Don't tell me you're tired already! |It's time to let these Royals witness the tactics and teamwork of the Iron Blood! Heheh~
401251.unlock: Even at the beach, we cannot afford to be careless! Commander, have you adequately prepared for today's activities?
401251.drop_descrip: Even at the beach, we cannot afford to be careless! Commander, have you adequately prepared for today's activities?
401251.home: Commander, which girl are you staring at this time?

107068.detail: As long as you are around, no matter how tough a battle I endure or how great the pain I suffer from being separated from you, I’ll go on with hope that I’ll finally be with you.
107068.touch: Hmm, I like you the same way that you like me.
107068.main: Would you like to try my cooking tonight? Vestal said that I've already mastered her cooking skills...I am not that kind of girl who solely exists on the battlefield |nil| Because of you, I started to believe that one day this war will past and people will smile happily again.
107068.unlock: How, how does it look? Do I look a bit strange... no, of course I like it. I'd say every girl dreams about this day, just that...
107068.drop_descrip: How, how does it look? Do I look a bit strange... no, of course I like it. I'd say every girl dreams about this day, just that...

105090.detail: Commander... Can you take your eyes off me?
105090.touch: Commander, please don't touch the main gun that I was just using, you will affect my shooting accuracy.
105090.login: Commander, you’ve rested long enough. When shall we weigh anchor?
105090.battle: I will not allow you to misbehave anymore... All guns, ready to fire a volley!
105090.hp_warning: The bridge was hit? Damage control, now!
105090.feeling2: I’m proud of my BIG SEVEN title. Unfortunately the battleship era is closing, and a new wave of ships are arriving...
105090.mission_complete: Commander, mission reward has been delivered.
105090.main: Commander, although aircraft carriers are really powerful, but battleships are not obsolete. They are indispensable! |Amelia... She was a great woman, though she still cannot be found. Perhaps she is flying freely in another world... |My poor sisters were hurt on that humiliating day. One day, I will have those invaders pay for what they have done!
105090.feeling5: The Commander's compliment after the end of each battle is something which I crave for. Commander, can you... praise me a little more?
105090.upgrade: Emm, as one of the BIG SEVEN, my powers are unquestionable. Although, timely enhancements are still a necessity.
105090.unlock: Are you the one calling me? Well, I've been waiting for this day for a long. In the name of the BIG SEVEN, Eagle Union battleship Colorado, reporting in.
105090.feeling4: The Commander is willing to talk to someone as bad-tempered as me. Such a weirdo... I don't hate talking to the Commander, though.
105090.feeling1: Commander, please… don’t come any closer.
105090.propose: Unknowingly I’ve slowly become more dependent on you, Commander. With the power of the BIG SEVEN, I shall protect you until my dying breath.
105090.drop_descrip: Colorado class battleship— Colorado, hull number BB-45
105090.skill: It's time to show you the true power of the BIG SEVEN!
105090.profile: I'm the lead ship of the Colorado class. In order to gain an advantage in the decisive battle, I'm the first ship to be equipped with 406mm guns. BIG SEVEN... is the most honored title for us battleships.
105090.touch2: Shall I load the Commander into a 406mm gun and fire him?
105090.mission: Whether you need fire support or fleet battle, please give the order Commander.
105090.home: Making sure everyone returns home safely is also one of my duties.
105090.win_mvp: Huh? Am I the MVP? Such a piece of cake for one of the BIG SEVEN.
105090.expedition: A lot of oil and supplies have been shipped in. Looks like we got plenty of both for the next mission.
105090.mail: You’ve got new mail. There may be news from my sisters...
105090.feeling3: Commander, why do you care about me so much? Many people are afraid of me and keep their distance from me. Perhaps I've been too used to this. But recently, I’ve suddenly felt... so lonely.
105090.lose: This is not the end of the line...

900256.detail: Tell me when you're done inspecting.
900256.touch: You want someone to pamper you? ... You want ME to?
900256.login: For lunch, I'll make... Oh, Commander, are you going for a stroll?
900256.battle: Pretty tough, aren't you? You won't cry if I hit you, will you?
900256.hp_warning: ... So you want me to get serious?
900256.feeling2: How to get stronger? Uhh, do some push-ups? ... Not working for you?
900256.mission_complete: Ah, the rewards have arrived... Seems we can afford beef for dinner tonight.
900256.feeling5: I don't have any dreams. But I have the power to grant them. Commander, do you have a dream for me to grant one day?
900256.unlock: Hm? Ah... my turn to speak. I'm Massachusetts. I'm just a regular old South Dakota-class you can find anywhere... So, yeah, I hope we can... get along.
900256.feeling4: I like how cool you look when you're pushing yourself hard... but overdoing it isn't good. I'll force you to rest if I have to.
900256.feeling1: Your body is weak, Commander. Are you eating properly?
900256.propose: Umm, yeah... I already know what you want to do and want to say... Because I love you too, Commander.
900256.drop_descrip: South Dakota-class battleship – Massachusetts, Hull Number BB-59.
900256.touch2: ... If you'd move your body more, you'd have fewer weird thoughts.
900256.mission: So many missions waiting on us...
900256.home: You're back... Did you get hurt? If anyone pokes fun at you, we can talk about it.
900256.win_mvp: It's over already? But I was just warming up... Aren't there any other enemies left?
900256.expedition: ... Oh, look. They've brought so much back. I'll go help them out.
couple_encourage: The way you are now... I like it. This is good.
I envy your defense, sis...
900256.mail: I'll leave your letter here. Check it later.
900256.feeling3: Seeing you challenging yourself with things you can't do is... interesting. It makes me want to explore my own limits, too.

499040.detail: I don't understand. Why are all the people at this base so at ease?
499040.touch: Yes? Has there been a change of plans?
499040.login: Excellent, you're back. Have you finished work our next plan yet, Commander?
499040.hp_warning: Carry out emergency damage control plan!
499040.feeling2: Names and titles are no proof of strength, that much is true. But that is fine. As time passes, you learn how futile your concerns are.
499040.mission_complete: Mission successful. Let us get started on the next one, Commander.
499040.main: One day, I hope to meet the Scharnhorst sisters myself.|Sometimes, things don't go as planned. You must think carefully before committing yourself to anything, Commander.|Don't blame others over things that are out of their control. Nobody can predict the future.
499040.feeling5: I do not approve of being reliant on someone. Excessive intimacy is a hindrance in war, clouding one's judgment and forming obstacles to one's plans... Ah, I can't believe what I'm saying...
499040.upgrade: With strength, one can reduce the number of irregularities in a plan.
499040.unlock: Are you the one who summoned me here? I am Odin. I hereby take up post as your tactician.
499040.feeling4: We make a fine pair, both in the office and the war room. But that can backfire, as I may end up becoming reliant on you...
499040.feeling1: I am not even disappointed, I simply wonder how someone as lousy as you became a commander in the first place.
499040.propose: Understood. I shall continue to provide assistance for you, whenever– Hey, wait a minute... Th-this isn't what you said would happen! ...No, that's not to say I oppose this! I just wasn't... mentally prepared... What I'm getting at is: give me a moment to think!
499040.skill: You wasted your last chance to turn back!
499040.profile: I am the battleship Odin. I existed only within the realm of the Iron Blood navy's imagination. Destiny has brought me here to serve under you and assist in the realization of your goals.
499040.touch2: Y-you will hear from me at the court martial!
499040.mission: You have missions. Leaving them unfinished would be a foolish choice.
499040.home: Commander, we are in all-out war; we cannot afford to rest.
499040.win_mvp: Victory was ours since before the battle began.
499040.expedition: The commission team has returned. Excellent, exactly as was planned.
499040.mail: Mail has arrived. Could it be new intelligence?
499040.feeling3: Mourn for my fallen comrades? If I were to stop and mourn for every lost soul, I would never win the war.
499040.lose: Impossible... My plan should have been flawless...!

900251.detail: Hmm, you want to know how well I fight?
900251.touch: Don’t touch me as if you’re trying to be intimate with me.
900251.login: Welcome back... how does my smile look? (Forcibly smiles)
900251.hp_warning: I won't let go of victories to my enemies!
900251.feeling2: What must I do to possess a good smile... think about the things I like? If so, I feel very happy even at the thought of winning against South Dakota... muahahaha...
900251.mission_complete: Go grab the reward yourself, I’m not interested.
900251.upgrade: It feels so good to become stronger.
900251.unlock: Hello, Commander, I am Washington... my sister told me that I cannot be so rough once I join the fleet, so I am practicing my smile. Darn, why must I listen to her...
900251.feeling4: Lately, my smile has become more natural? Emm, huh (scratches head), I was recently trying to find a new hobby. While I was searching, I realized that being with you is not so bad… (whispers)
900251.feeling1: You are too weak, it’s no fun playing with you, go practice some more.
900251.propose: Wait wait! We’re doing “that”, right? Is this your new way of teasing me!... Damn, you bastard, I’m not sure if I should cry or laugh about this...
900251.drop_descrip: North Carolina class battleship— Washington, hull number BB-56.
900251.skill: Out of my way. I'm ready to fight!
900251.profile: North Carolina class ship no. 2. I am Washington! The thing I like to do the most is to destroy my enemies. Recently, I am practicing on my smile. —— Battle record? I don’t really show off with such things, all in all, how’s my smile?
900251.mission: A new mission? Haha, now my blood is boiling.
900251.home: I’m glad that you didn’t get hurt—— What?! I don’t have feelings for you!
900251.win_mvp: Sure enough, I am happiest when all the foes are annihilated~
900251.expedition: Your memory can’t be worse than mine, right? The commission fleet has returned, won’t you go greet them?
900251.feeling3: No, no, that’s not right. If we do it this way, won’t it end much the same like in the past? … Don’t try so hard? You sometimes say stuff like that… Hmm? That was a good smile from me just now?
900251.lose: Oh, I will not forget you!

900250.detail: Being stared like that makes a bit shy...
900250.touch: Do you need help with something?
900250.battle: Don’t be overconfident, and try not to be so nervous while focusing on winning~
900250.feeling2: Commander remembers me~ Not that I’m boasting or anything, but I still have confidence in my low sense of existence. (smiles wryly)
900250.mission_complete: The mission rewards were sent out, are you not going to pick it up?
900250.upgrade: I'll try to work a bit harder~
900250.unlock: North Carolina here, awaiting your dispatch. Although I may seem to have a bland personality compared to my sisters. But as the saying goes, no personality is still a personality, hehe. Anyways, awaiting your orders, sir.
900250.feeling4: I always believe there is nothing wrong with being ordinary. But after meeting you Commander, I want to change myself a little... after all, my sisters are all so charismatic~ Well.. Commander, are you fond of bunny girls?~
900250.propose: Well, your trust deserves to be rewarded... umm... Commander, do you like bunny girls?~
900250.drop_descrip: North Carolina class battleship— North Carolina, hull number BB-55.
900250.mission: It’s not good to leave tasks unfinished.
900250.home: Ah, hold on, your collar is all messed up. Stand still while I fix it... there you go~ (waves).
900250.win_mvp: If the Commander gives me a few praises, then I will be very happy~
900250.expedition: The commission is over, they should be back soon~
900250.feeling3: If you’re only going by appearances, every child in this fleet looks cute. But in terms of personality, they all have their unique quirks. To be honest, I am a bit envious of them. (strokes chin).
900250.lose: Not so successful... let's try again next time.

10400040.detail: Are you here to play a game, Commander? I was just about to start streaming one, actually! Would you like to play it with me?
10400040.touch: You wanna play a round with me? Certainly! I accept your challenge! My skill should not be underestimated!
10400040.login: You haven't forgotten about the monthly check in, right? That'd be a real noob move!
10400040.feeling2: It's not easy to be a streamer. I try as hard as possible, but people still call me a noob... What should I do to get better?
10400040.mission_complete: Mission complete! Let's see what we got! Hm? What's up, Ikazuchi? You what? Secretaries can't collect mission rewards?!
10400040.main: Maybe I'll host the Kizuna AI Cup here! Ayanami and Long Island said they'd be down, so why not be our 4th player, Commander?|Being a genius but in reality playing like a total noob is suffering...|Whoosh! What do you think about this pose I learned from Jamaica? Don't I look cool?
10400040.feeling5: You're such a good game explainer, Commander! You know about all sorts of games, and nobody will call me a noob A.I. with you by my side! ... I'm counting on you, Commander!
10400040.unlock: HAI DOMO! Virtual Gamer Kizuna AI here! Don't worry, Commander, I've played AL a whole bunch before! ... Wait, I've become a ship now?!
10400040.feeling4: Damn it all! Why are my horror game streams so popular?! I have you to thank for suggesting it, but... please suggest a less scary game next time!
10400040.propose: You got this ring just for me, didn't you? I'm so happy! Er! Actually, I meant I'm really grateful! ... I can't wait to hear you talk about games every day from now on! And thanks for all your help!
10400040.drop_descrip: HAI DOMO! Virtual Gamer Kizuna AI here! Don't worry, Commander, I've played AL a whole bunch before! ... Wait, I've become a ship now?!
10400040.profile: My hair? Heheh, I'm virtual so I can change my hair's length whenever I want. How else do you think I look this cool while I'm fraggin' out? I'm the super gamer version of Kizuna AI! Check it!
10400040.touch2: Commander, do you know what a "headshot" is? Mind if I perform one on you?
10400040.mission: Mission located! Let's do tons of them so we'll earn a boatload of money!
10400040.home: Great performance, Commander! Huh? You want a lap pillow? ... Fine, fine. Inazuma babies you too much. Whatever, go ahead and let your guard down. Inazuma, do the next one for me.
10400040.win_mvp: A winner is me! I'm the MVP!
10400040.expedition: The commission team is back. Start another one immediately! We don't want to waste time!
couple_encourage: Eugen, I'll cover you!
10400040.mail: Hey, we've got mail! Maybe it's a present from the publishers!
10400040.feeling3: Huh? Stream a horror game? No, I don't want to... I really, really, really don't want to!
10400040.lose: Okay, I'm getting ticked off now! I'm not forgetting this, ever!

499041.detail: I don't understand. Why are all the people at this base so at ease? ...No, it is simply I who is always trying too hard.
499041.login: It is good to see you again. You ought to dedicate your days off to your own hobbies, Commander.
499041.main: Gneisenau, enjoyment of the arts will always elude you if you only think in statistics. You stand to learn from Scharnhorst in that regard.|Lord Tirpitz, whereabouts is Lord Bismarck? Forsooth, 'tis reassuring to know that thou knoweth. I shan't inquire further.|Plum trees and snow... This is an unfamiliar, but picturesque sight that I will likely never forget.
499041.unlock: I thought I would never have time to pursue the fine arts, and yet here I am now. Your thoughts, Commander? Eastern as this calligraphy may be, does it not suit the connotations of my name?
499041.drop_descrip: I thought I would never have time to pursue the fine arts, and yet here I am now. Your thoughts, Commander? Eastern as this calligraphy may be, does it not suit the connotations of my name?
499041.touch2: Stop it! I am trying to focus here!
499041.home: To fight is to put one's whole being into something, be that firing volleys on the battlefield or turning a blank canvas into a masterpiece.

301262.touch: I have to tell my sister about all the customs I learned from the Dragon Empery!
301262.login: Welcome back, Commander. I'm about to go wish my sister a happy new year, as is customary in the Dragon Empery... Would you like to come with me?
301262.main: Do they eat New Year's rice cake in the Dragon Empery as well? Perhaps they just eat whatever they feel like eating. |A red envelope from you? Please don't forget to give one to my sister as well. |Commander, our dreams will come true this year... right? N-no, I'm sure they will!
301262.feeling5: My New Year's wish, huh? Um... if I had to say, it'd probably be to celebrate even more New Years with Commander and my sister...
301262.unlock: The Dragon Empery's New Year celebrations and new outfits are sure to lift everyone's spirits~ My sister will probably love this new dress as well. What do you think, Commander?
301262.drop_descrip: The Dragon Empery's New Year celebrations and new outfits are sure to lift everyone's spirits~ My sister will probably love this new dress as well. What do you think, Commander?
301262.mail: I'll leave the mail that just arrived over here. I wonder if my sister sent me a greeting card?

900253.detail: Dost thy heart cry restlessly in my absence?
900253.touch: The night is both lengthy and brief. Come, blow out the light burning within thee, and accompany me into the dark.
900253.login: O unclean snake, who is it thee lusts after today?
900253.battle: Sinful roses of blood, bloom around me! Bloom!
900253.hp_warning: Perhaps I have indulged myself too much...
900253.feeling2: What a nice gaze. Through thy pupils, I can see another world.
900253.mission_complete: Only the moon and sweet liquor fail to disappoint. We shall share the most unforgettable of nights.
900253.feeling5: O ignorant snake, hast thou only realised now, how long I have hopelessly been in love with thee? Therefore... would thou give thy everything to me?
900253.upgrade: Did thou hear? A sound that makes my blood boil, like wind passing through the forest in the dead of night.
900253.unlock: I see. So the scent that has been driving me crazy... emanates from thy soul. O sinful Commander who tempts me so, engrave my name upon thine heart - Duke of York, of the Royal Navy.
900253.feeling4: How unfathomable... looking at thy sleeping visage hast made me replete with calmness... Now, pray that thou dost not wake, for I know not what I would do to thee...
900253.feeling1: It would appear... that I must get a little more violent...
900253.propose: Even the most ingenious poet cannot describe the beauty of this moment. Hehe, close thy eyes, feel my warmth, and listen to the beating of my heart. This is the one who shall be thy lifelong partner...
900253.drop_descrip: King George V-class battleship - HMS Duke of York.
900253.skill: All ye, weep at your own demise!
900253.profile: I am King George V-class' Duke of York. Scharnhorst? An interesting one indeed, but now, thou art the one who captures my interest the most... My... if thou displays such an expression to me, I won't be able to contain myself...
900253.touch2: Ahh, how beautiful... thy eyes, normally placid, burning with the fires of lust...
900253.mission: Such fair weather is rare indeed. 'twould be a pity to return to port so soon.
900253.home: Oh, triumphant nightingale that has overcome death itself, what plagues thee enough to silence thy song?
900253.win_mvp: There exists no living being that can resist the embrace of death.
900253.expedition: O mesmerising Narcissus, do remember my warning when greeting those who return. Be misled not by the illusions swirling in the water.
couple_encourage: Karma shall find thee one day.
Stop struggling in futility, my~ little~ kitten~
900253.mail: Thy visage when reading and concentrating, unbudging and focused, resembles one of Michelangelo's sculptures. I do not dislike such determination.
900253.feeling3: How thy visage tempts me so with each passing moment... I must ask of thee, just how sweet is thy blood?
900253.lose: Ahh... why dost thou obstinately refuse to obey me...

299020.detail: You are the one and only being who matters to me... Until I met you, there was nary a single soul who believed in me.
299020.login: Splendid; you're back. I, Monarch, am superior to the likes of Wales and York. Wouldn't you agree, Commander?
299020.battle: Depend on me! I will make sure this fleet returns home without as much as a scratch!
299020.hp_warning: If Wales were me, she would probably have sunk long ago.
299020.feeling2: I only survived in that dark world by believing that I am excellence itself, and thus irreplaceable...
299020.mission_complete: For as long as I exist, it isn't over. I am excellence itself, therefore I must exist.
299020.main: Wales and York... I despise them for bereaving me of my existence, but I cannot resent them for succeeding me.|A younger sister? If I have one, her name would be... Prince of Wales... That has a rather nice ring to it.|I will make the world understand how foolish it was not to choose me.
299020.feeling5: Commander, to me, you are the most special, most dear person in existence. You always have, and always will be...
299020.upgrade: Hmph, sure enough, I am the most excellent of the King George V class.
299020.unlock: We meet for the first time. I am the battleship Monarch. Hmph, once I was discarded, but now I am needed; how ironic... Is this how low the Royal Navy has sunk?
299020.feeling4: So, they can still laugh together... Perhaps I wasn't discarded for nought, then... I have never felt this way before.
299020.feeling1: Are you saying that I am inferior to them?!
299020.propose: Even if the world no longer needs me, you will always need me. That is more than enough for me... Hahah, perhaps I was materialised with the sole purpose of meeting you. Even if so... I am happy.
299020.skill: Not even the Queen's orders can subdue me!
299020.profile: I am the battleship named Monarch, one of the rejected King George V-class designs. Hmph, though I was once forgotten, now I live and breathe...
299020.touch2: Do not fall victim to those degenerate habits of theirs.
299020.mission: Let me handle this mission. I shall prove my excellence!
299020.home: That was a marvellous welcome. Hmph, were I the only one returning, would anyone welcome me at all...?
299020.win_mvp: Heed my words: depend on me! I will always win!
299020.expedition: I wonder what efforts it took to materialise me... Hmph, regardless, I will see to it they are repaid in double.
couple_encourage: I am George, Elizabeth, and Edward... but I will never be "Wales"!
In another world, perhaps I would've been your real big sister.
299020.mail: You've received mail regarding the war. You would do best to check it.
299020.feeling3: Love needs no repayment. No matter how much the Royal Family neglects me, my loyalty to them is unwavering.
299020.lose: Am I... being discarded yet again?

102182.drop_descrip: Merry Sweetsmas, Commander! Today, I get to eat as many sweets as I want without anyone saying things about it~♪ Hmm, I already eat this much every day? I guess so~

900252.detail: Want to look at my medal collection?
900252.login: You've come. If it's fighting, I'm ready for it any time.
900252.feeling2: It is my wish to live honestly and sincerely. That's why I'll speak my mind if I have something to say. You too should do the same without holding back.
900252.feeling5: What do you want to do after the war? --Me? I'll probably stick with you. I feel the safest out of battle when I'm with you. Will you... take me along with you?
900252.upgrade: I will show you... what lies at the end of power
900252.unlock: Second ship of the Yorktown class, Enterprise, reporting for duty. I will neither sympathize nor hold back with my enemies, and instead, I go all out. Such is my way.
900252.feeling4: There's no meaning in being peerless. As long as you are here, Commander, I can draw upon all of my strength. Let us end this war.
900252.profile: I am the Yorktown class aircraft carrier, Enterprise. "Grey Ghost" is one of the many nicknames I have. My smoke-covered and bloodstained battle record is a reminder of my mission. I will continue to be victorious until the war ends.
900252.feeling1: ...Commander, you don't seem to have enough courage
900252.propose: I carry with me the hopes and wills of the countless battlefields and goodbyes that I have experienced. Commander, are you prepared to shoulder them all? …I see. Then let us walk together until the end of our lives.
900252.drop_descrip: Yorktown-class aircraft carrier ー Enterprise, Hull Number CV-6!
900252.mission: Commander, your missions are not yet completed.  Hurry up and set off!
900252.home: It's one battle after another, huh...
900252.win_mvp: Commander, tell me. How many more do I have to sink?
900252.expedition: I've been on the battlefield for a long time, so I know about the importance of logistics. Commander, let's greet the girls who work hard behind the scenes.
900252.feeling3: All the lights in the sky are stars, just as all the lights on the seas are enemies... Commander, will there be a day where there's no more fighting?
900252.lose: I've lost after giving my all. I'm not regretting this...

399020.detail: If you've got time to stare at me then maybe do your work instead.
399020.touch: Commander, you don't have the free time to endlessly chat with me.
399020.login: Late, as always. Just how long will you keep me waiting?
399020.battle: All ships, form up! Target: enemies in front!
399020.feeling2: This blade is my other half. Casually touch it, and you'll get hurt.
399020.mission_complete: Mission complete... Good lord, would you ever have realized it on your own?
399020.main: A blade requires careful maintenance. Isn't that obvious?|Sisters... eh. The Izumo class consists of just me, so I guess I'm a bit jealous.|Become stronger, Commander. Once you become strong enough to protect everyone... Once that happens, I...
399020.feeling5: The path of my blade is one of constant solitude... or so I thought. Hmph, maybe being with you... isn't so bad after all.
399020.unlock: Battleship Izumo, reporting in. Are you the Commander? Sure don't look very reliable... Listen here: do anything to slow me down, and you won't hear the end of it!
399020.feeling4: Hey, you've started getting just a bit into shape recently... Hmph, I suppose I'll acknowledge you've worked hard.
399020.feeling1: You lack what it takes to order me to swing this blade.
399020.propose: You're making that miserable face again. I just can't leave you be, huh... Listen, today is the day I will acknowledge your hard work... or, should I say, your talent! I, battleship Izumo, swear on my blade to walk with you, both in life and death.
399020.skill: Feel the wrath of my blade!
399020.profile: I'm battleship Izumo, of the Sakura Empire. I existed as a proposed Yamato-class design, although they didn't construct me... But if you look down me even slightly then prepare to taste one of my main cannon volleys.
399020.mission: What are you planning to do about these unfinished missions?
399020.home: Look who's back. Time's precious, so start reflecting on your last sortie immediately.
399020.expedition: Commission complete. Why don't you go on one yourself, sometime?
399020.mail: Here's a letter. It's rude to the sender to not read their letter thoroughly. Don't you agree?
399020.feeling3: *Sigh*... Why do you always make that miserable face, Commander? It's so miserable that... it makes me want to scold you...

10400020.detail: Please, feel at ease. Although my elegant uniform may steal your attention, I am still very much the intelligent super A.I. Kizuna AI I have always been.
10400020.touch: Please, do you not know uncouth it is to touch a lady nonchalantly?
10400020.login: Welcome back, Commander. Soon it will be time for our scheduled meeting. Let's get a lot of work done today.
10400020.battle: Please, everyone take care as to not be injured.
10400020.hp_warning: Something as trivial as this... will not defeat an intelligent super A.I.!
10400020.feeling2: I make strenuous efforts each day to be a mature A.I. so I may relate to everyone.
10400020.mission_complete: A mission has been completed. Let us go and collect our rewards now!
10400020.main: Commander, Hood invited me to a tea party. Would you perhaps like to attend it as well?|Formal attire certainly aids one's composure... Belfast, if you don't mind, would you kindly teach me the Royal Navy's etiquette?|Commander, would it be agreeable with you if I uploaded videos from this base? I am quite talented at video making, you see.
10400020.feeling5: It is thanks to you that I have matured so much! I sincerely believe it would not have been possible without your help! ... Thank you so much!
10400020.upgrade: Installation complete! Pardon, I meant to proclaim that I have become smarter.
10400020.unlock: Well met. I'm Kizuna AI, the new addition to your base. I will do all in my power to be at least of some use. It is a pleasure meeting you, Commander.
10400020.feeling4: I can simply learn things instantly with a plugin? Oh, please, it isn't that simple! Even an A.I. must work hard!
10400020.feeling1: Can I just drop the act now?
10400020.propose: I am who I am now because of you... I believe I can relate to more people if I am with you. So... may I stay by your side for the foreseeable future, Commander?
10400020.drop_descrip: Well met. I'm Kizuna AI, the new addition to your base. I will do all in my power to be at least of some use. It is a pleasure meeting you, Commander.
10400020.profile: I am the embodyment of cuteness and etiquette! Please, enjoy the splendor of this smarter and more refined Kizuna AI!
10400020.touch2: You are guilty. There is no room for alternate interpretations. You are guilty.
10400020.mission: Commander, a new mission has appeared. Let us begin on our preparations at once!
10400020.home: Phew... Kinda tiring to act refined and all... Huh?! Commander?! H-how long have you been here...? My tone of voice sounded odd? No, not all, you must be imagining things! Ohohoho!
10400020.win_mvp: Gotta hand it to myself: I'm perfectly suited for combat, too!
10400020.expedition: I have pressing information. The commission team has returned. Let us swiftly head out to receive them!
couple_encourage: Takao, let us dispense retribution unto the forces of evil!
10400020.mail: Mail has arrived. It may be of urgent importance, so please do read it immediately.
10400020.feeling3: As I thought, there are more things I must learn in order to relate to everyone...! Commander, please grant me your guidance and support!
10400020.lose: How could an intelligent super A.I. like myself lose...

900247.detail: The melody of my flute is a requiem for the dead. Shall I play it for you?
900247.login: Intelligence is said to be a woman’s virtue, but that often puts me at odds with those senpai of mine. How troublesome~
900247.battle: The perfected aircraft carrier, {namecode:95}, setting sail!
900247.hp_warning: Pump water to the other side! Hurry!
900247.feeling2: My sister {namecode:96} and I held on for two years during the darkest of times. If only our senpai could have worked a little bit harder.
900247.mission_complete: We’re not going to carry out our plans of attrition warfare? Tch~
900247.feeling5: Commander, could you lend me your shoulder? Sometimes, even I want to simply clear my mind and rest. When I get like that, can I depend on you to be by my side?
900247.unlock: As the flagship of the Fifth Carrier Division, I, Shoukaku, shall do my best to become as good as those esteemed senpai in the First Carrier Division, or something... *giggles* That was on purpose~
900247.feeling4: Those senpai are so sly! Just when I was about to overtake them, they went somewhere I could never reach! How unfair!
900247.feeling1: I think I just saw a future in which you were cut down by {namecode:91}, Commander.
900247.propose: The melody of my flute is like a flowing river, requiring an inspiration that usually can only be found atop a mountain. Just being by your side, however, inspires me even more.
900247.drop_descrip: First ship of the {namecode:95}-class aircraft carriers, {namecode:95}.
900247.skill: This is the privilege of being the elder sister!
900247.touch: Commander, would you like to hear me play my flute?
900247.touch2: Commander, come and indulge yourself in {namecode:95}'s tenderness.
900247.mission: Let me take a look the mission... It’s not the Coral Sea? That’s too bad~
900247.home: The girls have returned safely to port, just like the Fifth Carrier Division always does.
900247.win_mvp: The Glory of the 5th Carrier Divison is here! *giggles*
900247.expedition: This is all required to carry out the Circle Five Plan.
900247.mail: We’ve got mail from HQ, they told us to carry out the Decisive Battle Doctrine. Heh, just kidding~!
900247.feeling3: Do I hold a grudge against the First and Second Carrier Divisions? Of course~ For them to leave us behind like that, wouldn’t anyone complain in that situation?
900247.lose: Hiryuu-senpai may be willing to fight until the bitter end, but... that’s not my style. What a shame~

299021.detail: Stand up straight and puff out your chest, Commander. You're the only one I deign to— You're not sure where to look? Well, why not look me in the eyes then?
299021.touch: You like this dress, do you? Hmph, I see you've learned the art of empty flattery from Wales. But nonetheless... thank you...
299021.login: Don't just stand there gawking, Commander. There remains much to be done today.
299021.battle: Allow me to demonstrate the elegance with which a lady of the Royal Navy comports herself.
299021.main: nil|Shall I teach you the Royal Navy's courtly dances?|Such splendid dress is normally reserved for special occasions. But for me, every day I exist is a day to be celebrated.
299021.unlock: Hmph. One's outfit is merely superficial. True nobility must come from within. Don't you agree, Commander?
299021.drop_descrip: Hmph. One's outfit is merely superficial. True nobility must come from within. Don't you agree, Commander?
299021.touch2: I admire your bravery. Now would you rather I stab or trample you? Or would you prefer to taste a volley from my guns?

900246.detail: My duty is to support my big sister who is always charging too far ahead. Admittedly, it gets a little irritating at times.
900246.touch: Isn't it amazing how different people can come to different conclusions about the same topic?
900246.login: Welcome back. Ready to get back to work? I've prepared everything you need, Commander.
900246.battle: Truth only exists within the guns' range.
900246.hp_warning: All ships, remember to stay alert!
900246.feeling2: Is it urgent? I prefer simple and effective forms of communication.
900246.mission_complete: Rewards distributed. Please accept them when you have a moment.
900246.feeling5: The present flies by like an arrow, but the future always arrives too late. I hope that one day, I will be able to see the future that you and I create.
900246.upgrade: It's fine as long as you haven't let power cloud your judgement...
900246.unlock: Hello, Commander, I'm Gneisenau. Though my big sister is a bit reckless, we're actually an invincible team. I hope I will be able to sail with her as often as possible!
900246.feeling4: Without realizing it, I've come to enjoy supporting both my sister and you, Commander.
900246.feeling1: I assumed you were more intelligent, Commander...
900246.propose: A promise, huh? Long ago, I would have despised the notion of being tied down to emotions... but it doesn't seem so bad now.
900246.touch2: Commander, Anton is locked on, you can't escape now.
900246.mission: A mission? Let me do some planning for you...
900246.home: Welcome back. Please take it easy for a while.
900246.win_mvp: Sorry, this is war. There's no room for mercy.
900246.expedition: A commission has been completed! Care to inspect the results?
900246.mail: Commander, there's mail for you. I'll leave it here.
900246.feeling3: "The Ugly Sisters..." Though we were given that epithet for our achievements, it still hurts a little. Commander, do you think I'm ugly?

399021.detail: My name has connections to classical dancing...? I-I see...
399021.touch: ... Drunk? Me? I've only had a few... *Hick*
399021.battle: I'll remind ya, in case ya forgot...! I'm the battleship Izumo!
399021.main: Dancing and my sword are much alike. Untold hours of learning and practice are for a single moment of brilliance...|Commander, if I really captivate you so... will you be able to finish your work?|Savory delicacies and mature festivities... I say why not enjoy the New Year and let loose for once? Hahahah!
399021.unlock: You'd like to see my classical dance? Your tastes are quite refined, Commander... In that case, I'll show you the finest performance in the land!
399021.drop_descrip: You'd like to see my classical dance? Your tastes are quite refined, Commander... In that case, I'll show you the finest performance in the land!
399021.touch2: Commander, are you insinuating you want a swift kick?
399021.win_mvp: How stunning; how gorgeous – to my eyes, the sight of this battlefield is worth ten thousand ryo.

900249.login: Milord, milord! What shall we do today?
900249.battle: Everyone, go~! Waaah?! My guns fired on accident!
900249.feeling2: Milord, come play with me! Ah... I forgot to bring stuff to play with... what should we do?
900249.mission_complete: Milord, milord! I've brought the rewards... Oops!
900249.feeling5: I know how hard my big sister works, so for her sake, I know that I should allow myself to be happy. That way, I can share my happiness with her. Now that you are here, Milord, I think I'll finally be able to do that. I feel so happy every time I see you!
900249.unlock: Woah! It's Milord! Milord in person! Um... I'm Yamahi-, {namecode:79}! I am pleased to make your acquaintance.
900249.feeling4: Your Majesty, do you know this mask? It's a fox mask used in Kagura. Hehe, I'm actually about to practice my Kagura dance now. Do you want to watch?
900249.feeling1: You're so boring, Milord. I don't want to play with you anymore.
900249.propose: Milord? You're going to give this to me? ...Even though I am slow-footed and far from perfect? Milord, you are far too kind. I love you too.
900249.touch2: Woah! Watch out, Milord! I'm about to fire my main gun!
900249.home: Welcome back, Milord, I made you some tea... Woah! Watch out!
900249.win_mvp: Milord, did you see that? Did you?
900249.expedition: Milord, the girls have returned from commissions!
900249.mail: Milord! Milord! Your mail is here!
900249.feeling3: I love my sister, but she's a bit too quiet sometimes. Milord, I like spending time with you more because you'll play with me!

107071.detail: It's a party, you gotta eat a lot! What if you eat too much? "No problem, just work out and sweat it off later!" How's my Enty impression?
107071.touch: Is this dress gonna make you fall in love with me all over again? Ahahaha!
107071.login: Heyyy♪ Commander, I'm looking pretty hot tonight, huh?
107071.main: This one's Enty's, this one's Yorktown's, this one's Northampton's, this one's... oh, it's yours, Commander! Exactly one bottle. Pretty nice, huh?|So I have to dress up like this for the party? Aren't you worried I'm gonna be a fish out of water in there?|I'm not expecting anyone to call me the belle of the ball tonight. Not while everyone else is dressed up all pretty-like. What? You think I give up too easily?
107071.unlock: Congratulations! You did it, Commander! Now let's pop the champagne and celebrate! It's party time!
107071.drop_descrip: Congratulations! You did it, Commander! Now let's pop the champagne and celebrate! It's party time!
107071.touch2: Turns out I'm pretty different from my sisters, huh...?

900248.detail: That Grey Ghost... I’d like to duel her just once.
900248.login: Where are we going today? Pearl Harbor? Or perhaps the Coral Sea?
900248.battle: A never-ending swarm of enemies? I’m already used to it.
900248.feeling2: Seniors and juniors... they’re all such a pain.
900248.mission_complete: Hmm... Seems like the situation has taken a turn for the better!
900248.main: {namecode:95} is so cute when she’s embarrassed!|Keep fighting until the last arrow is broken! That is what it means to be an elite!|Wait, Grey Ghost, don’t run away just because you won! Let’s have a rematch!
900248.feeling5: Commander, you make me feel just as if I am with Shoukaku. H-huh? That’s not it! I’m not treating you as my sister!
900248.upgrade: As a perfected aircraft carrier, I shall not lose to anyone, not even to my seniors or to the Grey Ghost herself.
900248.unlock: I am {namecode:96}, the last elite of the Sakura Empire’s Carrier Divisions. I can only be at my best when I am with my sister {namecode:95}.
900248.feeling4: Whenever I feel irritated or lost, training always makes me feel at ease. Yes, I’ll definitely get stronger and catch up to that Grey Ghost one day.
900248.feeling1: Commander, would you like a taste of the anguish I experienced during the Battle of the Marianas?
900248.propose: E-eh?! Th-this is... I’m not misunderstanding you, right? Then... um, from now on, I’ll be in your care, dar... darling? Waaah! Shoukaku is calling me!
900248.drop_descrip: Second ship of the {namecode:95}-class aircraft carriers, {namecode:96}.
900248.skill: As long as Shoukaku is with me~!
900248.touch: My least favorite food? Turkey, of course.
900248.mission: Is it time for a break? Commander, you should come try some of {namecode:95}’s cooking!
900248.home: I’ll need you to perform some maintenance on me. Ah, don’t forget about the planes either!
900248.win_mvp: I am the auspicious crane, after all!
900248.expedition: If only I had more planes...!
900248.mail: So? Is it good news or bad news?
900248.feeling3: My fate always seems to be entertwined with Lexington’s... Ah~ Commander, please don’t tell Sara I said that. I can’t handle that girl.
900248.lose: Am I going to be sunk... again...?

201140.detail: Commander, watch me, watch me! I don't become dizzy no matter how many times I spin myself! Amazing, right? Praise me, praise me~!
201140.touch: Hehe... That tickles! I'm going to tickle you back, Commander!
201140.login: Commander, Commander, you're so slow! What took you so long? Hurry up, let's go have some fun!
201140.battle: Let's ram~! The first one to fall will play the punishment game later~
201140.feeling2: The great Glowworm is the strongest!
201140.mission_complete: Yahoo! So many rewards! Don't mind if we do!
201140.main: Hey there, you defenseless commander, eat my Glowworm CQC! Unya! Ah, I stubbed my toe...|Stay still, the cola is going to overflow. I'm gonna drink it before it makes a mess! *chugs*|Commander, do you think we can make a whirlpool if we spin on the water fast enough?
201140.feeling5: I give up! I like you lots and lots! I don't care if I'm made fun of (Glowworm headbutts you), so be thankful!
201140.upgrade: I, Glowworm, have become even stronger!
201140.unlock: Hello! I am the Royal Navy's G-class destroyer, Glowworm! Commander, want to play with me today? I'm pretty good at hide and seek!
201140.feeling4: Recently the Commander has been popping up in my dreams... I can't let him find out about this...
201140.feeling1: Even as the magnanimous Glowworm, I will not be giving any quarter to idiots!
201140.propose: You won't regret this, right? It's too late if you want to! ... Ehehe, hehehe. Then, say 'Glowworm is the cutest'! ...Say it. Say it even more!
201140.drop_descrip: G-class destroyer ー Glowworm, Hull Number H92!
201140.profile: I am G class' Glowworm! People say it's hard getting near me, but I actually like skinship engagements~! Commander, Commander, I am always energetic! W-whaa!
201140.touch2: Nnngggh! Damn you, perverted Commander! I'm gonna headbutt you! *donk*
201140.home: Tadaa! Now, give me a big hug!
201140.win_mvp: The enemies were idiots~ My courage is second to none, after all!
201140.expedition: I, Glowworm, have received tribute from the commission team!
couple_encourage: Three Musketeers, charge!
Tomato Squad, ramming speed!
201140.feeling3: I'm not gonna be 'cleared' by you Commander. Stupid, stu-pid!
201140.lose: Ah~! W-wait a minute! My fighting has just begun! I shall return!

102051.detail: St. Louis must've had a lot of fun making me try out so many clothes... Do you really think I look cute this way, Commander?
102051.touch: Huh? I was just thinking about what I should do during New Year's... There are so many things I want to do.
102051.login: It seems the New Year's spirit has swept over the entire fleet.
102051.main: My New Year's wish is... that I'll be more courageous and positive, and that no harm will come to any of my friends...|For this year's shrine visit, the whole Brooklyn-class, Cleveland, and her Knights of The Sea all went there together as one big family.|It's snowing... I never realized how peaceful and beautiful snow can be.
102051.feeling5: Commander? You don't have to worry about me. I was just thinking about how I now have friends and a sweetheart who I can celebrate the new year together with, and how unbelievably happy it makes me.
102051.unlock: I... want to be part of the new year festivities too. Oh, you don't have to worry about me. I'm no longer the fledgling I once was.
102051.drop_descrip: I... want to be part of the new year festivities too. Oh, you don't have to worry about me. I'm no longer the fledgling I once was.
102051.home: Let me be part of the mission, Commander. My SG would surely be good to have.
102051.win_mvp: That's right...! You did a great job, me!
102051.lose: It's okay, there's always the next time...!

101120.detail: Don't touch my radar! It's our most effective weapon against the enemy during the night!
101120.touch: I know what it is you really want to touch, weirdo!
101120.login: What tricks should we play on the other girls today, Commander? Heehee~!
101120.battle: I missed the Turkey Shoot last time, but this battle is mine!
101120.feeling2: You're still upset about that prank? You're no fun!
101120.mission_complete: I'll take these rewards off your hands if you don't want them, Commander!
101120.main: Commander, don't just stand there, come play with me!|Hahaha, look! Spence's reactions are so hilarious!|Since I don't know when I'll do something wrong, I'll just go ahead and apologize now.
101120.feeling5: Close your eyes, Commander~... *Kiss* Did you feel that? That wasn't me... Okay, it was!
101120.upgrade: Aha! I came up with a new prank!
101120.unlock: Hi there, Commander! I'm Thatcher. Want to play a game with me?
101120.feeling4: What would you do if I told you I liked you? Hehe, I'm just joking~!
101120.propose: Just so you know: you're totally wrong if you think my pranks will end just because I got this ring! My pranks are an expression of love. So, I'm expecting you to take~ good~ care~ of~ me~!
101120.drop_descrip: Fletcher-class destroyer - Thatcher, Hull Number DD-514!
101120.profile: I'm Thatcher from the Little Beavers. I'm named after Rear Admiral Henry K. Thatcher. Awesome, right? Aren't you surprised?
101120.touch2: Hoho? You wanna touch me there again?
101120.mission: The game isn't over yet. Don't be lazy!
101120.home: Good work, Commander! Want me to help you relax? Don't worry, I won't play any tricks on you~!
101120.expedition: Another commission complete! I sure hope the girls didn't run into any kamikazes.
101120.mail: You've got new mail! I-I'm not hiding it this time!
101120.feeling3: Commander, I want to always be able to play tricks on you, but... Do you hate me for that?
101120.lose: Damn it! My prank failed! Ahh, Spence, get outta the way, I'll end up bumping into you!

499030.detail: Achievements? ...Let's start racking them up today.
499030.touch: What's wrong? Do you want me to comfort you?
499030.login: Make sure that the wait was worth my time, Commander.
499030.hp_warning: Ugh, to think that my equipment wouldn't work...?!
499030.feeling2: Because I was born into this world, I shall accomplish something. Otherwise, I wouldn't be able to face those who designed me.
499030.mission_complete: How long... are you planning on ignoring the mission rewards?
499030.main: What do you think you're doing! Adding milk to coffee is nothing short of blasphemy! The same goes for sugar!!!|I can't believe it... though this room is so large, it doesn't even have a coffee maker...!|If only I were constructed in the Great War instead of being incarnated in this form, I wonder how much I would have been able to do... I guess thinking about it doesn't help.
499030.feeling5: Commander, I recognize you as the first and last commander I swear my loyalty to... But that's not all. You are the only one I've ever thought I wanted to get closer to.
499030.upgrade: Hm. Let's test this out in a real battle.
499030.unlock: Light cruiser, Mainz. You'll be my first Commander. Hmph. Don't you dare disappoint me.
499030.feeling4: At one point I fought to prove myself. However, I now fight for your sake. I want to prove to everyone else that you are a sufficiently reliable person.
499030.feeling1: To think that my first commander would be this pathetic... How depressing.
499030.propose: My existence is no longer just about battle. My life and fate have already been tied to yours. My beloved Commander, I henceforth pledge my heart to you for the rest of eternity.
499030.profile: Light cruiser, Mainz. There were plans for me to succeed the Admiral Hipper class, but due to circumstances, I've incarnated in this form. You get the rest without me telling you, right?
499030.touch2: Perfect. I can finish testing my guns by firing them at you.
499030.mission: Are you going to neglect all the missions?
499030.win_mvp: An expected outcome, given that I am here.
499030.expedition: The girls who went on commissions are returning. I'll be leaving my seat for a bit.
couple_encourage: Witness the true power of the Iron Blood!
499030.mail: There's new mail. There's no way you've forgotten, right?
499030.feeling3: If I am lacking in actual battle experience, there is nothing to do but humbly accumulate more. Commander, I won't mince words - please send me out on more battles.
499030.lose: Hm. I'll consider this as valuable practical experience.

101252.detail: How long do you plan to keep staring... The party's going to end at this rate! You dummy!
101252.touch: E-even if we're dancing, I won't forgive you if you touch any weird places!
101252.login: Commander, how long do you plan to keep me waiting?! Um... It, it's not like I went out of my way to show up early or anything!
101252.main: Woah... This is the first time I've seen Yorktown like that... Is she going to be okay?|That Sims... I bet she's hiding somewhere waiting to pull a prank on me... Commander, m-make sure to protect me!|Iroha is here as well?! ...Wh-whatever! Since I'm here with the commander, I'll let her slide this time!
