101252.feeling5: W-well, since you were on such good behavior during the party, you do deserve some praise. What should I do next... H-hey! Don't suddenly hug me...! Ugh... Jeez... Wh-what am I going to do with you...
101252.unlock: Hmph! I'm only here because you pleaded so desperately for me to come! Don't get any funny ideas! ...Why did I take so long to pick out my clothes? It... it's not like I was trying to impress anyone! I definitely wasn't looking forward to this party or anything!
101252.drop_descrip: Hmph! I'm only here because you pleaded so desperately for me to come! Don't get any funny ideas! ...Why did I take so long to pick out my clothes? It... it's not like I was trying to impress anyone! I definitely wasn't looking forward to this party or anything!
101252.touch2: Hello, naval police? Yes, it's that commander again, this time at the party...
101252.home: Good work... wh-what's your deal! Even I know when someone deserves praise!

899021.detail: Reliving one's childhood by enjoying games is one way to enjoy festivities. That being the case, I lack knowledge of the rules designated for these games...
899021.login: What I desire on the first day of the new year... a peaceful night's sleep, and a rainbow-colored dream that reflects my wishes.
899021.headtouch: Hm...? Did you want to know about my dreams...?
899021.main: Mountains, birds, fruits. All wonderful signs of a dream in which spring blooms forth.|Our connected memories spread out, like freshly-fallen powder snow, as our affected emotions are as if blown by the spring breeze. ...May these peaceful festivities spread much joy.|The Cardinal's favorite book was one recommended by me. Humans and ships alike desire to satisfy their curiosity...
899021.unlock: It is not against the teachings to halt one's pursuit of destiny and to surrender to the warm draft of festivities. It is mankind's prerogative to seek out auspicious portents.
899021.drop_descrip: It is not against the teachings to halt one's pursuit of destiny and to surrender to the warm draft of festivities. It is mankind's prerogative to seek out auspicious portents.
899021.touch2: Animals attempt to break their fetters in order to satiate their desires, whereas humans challenge taboos to satiate their curiosity.
899021.home: Please enlighten me. The significance of this festive garb, and the things I must do.

899020.detail: Whether your ambitions leads you into the wilderness of unparalleled achievements, the lofty spires of world domination, or the gardens of peaceful sanctuary, command me as would best serve your will.
899020.touch: The warmth and sensation of being touched... How exceedingly difficult to forget.
899020.login: Your orders, Commander. Whatever your will may be, I shall usher into reality.
899020.battle: Devote thyself not to the fleet― for that is my solemn charge.
899020.hp_warning: These scars will become my aegis.
899020.feeling2: This world is the surface of a calm lake— Disturbances may mar the waters with ripples, but peace must return in time.
899020.mission_complete: Only for the gardener whose blood nurtures the soil can the iris bloom in triumphant beauty.
899020.main: Commander, art thou pondering the meaning of life? Or perhaps...|The ebb and flow of tides are natural phenomena, and so are the flowing fates of humankind.|"Live, together with the fleet." Understood. I have received my newest directive from the Commander.
899020.feeling5: If those who are powerless resist fate, those with power cannot stand by and do nothing. Commander, your radiance, warmth, and affection—in order to protect all of this, I offer up my body and swear my love.
899020.upgrade: Even the most polished blade must eventually rot. That is to say, there is no point in chasing power.
899020.unlock: I am the personification of Champagne, part of the Iris Libre. Commander, please give me an order—a reason to exist.
899020.feeling4: Commander, there is no way for you to wear the rigging—armor, main guns, and torpedoes—that is required to defend the fleet. As I am a ship, I will take on the mission to protect you.
899020.feeling1: The hope you brought was but a false light. Why, Commander, must you torment me so?
899020.propose: Even if words stop existing, I will still listen to your voice. Even if the world loses its radiance, I will still look into your eyes. There is nothing in this world that can erase your existence from my heart. The warmth I've received from you, I shall repay with my eternal protection... These are my true feelings.
899020.skill: Sleep in the blue depths of the ocean...
899020.profile: Never have I received orders, nor have I ever accomplished anything. I am merely a blank slate—existing simply to become the delectable champagne presented to thee, the victor.
899020.touch2: Though your transgression may be slight, such conduct may turn others away from you.
899020.mission: The falcon that spreads not its wings cannot reach the sky. The ship that rows not its oars cannot not reach the other shore.
899020.home: Immerse yourself in the liberating quintessence of wine, for the mind requires reprieve. Man is naught without repose.
899020.win_mvp: I ensure that missions sown shall bear rich fruit.
899020.expedition: The birds' clarion call... It seems that our comrades have returned to us.
couple_encourage: Let us open our eyes to this colorful world.
Let us harken, for the world speaks.
899020.mail: A notice has arrived. Is it a joyous one, or is it a tragic one? Is it a desirable one, or a hateful one?
899020.feeling3: Trees bury their roots deep into the ground to avoid being blown away, and fish swim upstream to propagate their kind. Though they know they are fated to return to nothingness, living things defy their circumstances to the best of their ability.

201141.detail: Commander, you did something bad, didn't you~ Confess your crimes! Or else... Eh? You'll spend the day with me? Hmm, well then~ I guess I'll let you off the hook!
201141.touch: Where are the naughty girls?! Huh? Phrasing?
201141.login: Hrrm, you have kept Her Honour Judge Glowworm waiting... guilty Commander! Your sentence is to hang out with me more!
201141.main: Omaha! San Diego! Bring the bad guys to me! First up is... the Commander!|Hipper! Come play with meee! Or I sentence you to a headbutting!|Behold my headbutt of justice! ...Oof, I hit the wall. Waahh...
201141.unlock: Ahahaha! It is I, Glowworm, the impartial and absolute judge! Any wrongdoers will have me to answer to! Guilty verdicts will result in headbutts!
201141.drop_descrip: Ahahaha! It is I, Glowworm, the impartial and absolute judge! Any wrongdoers will have me to answer to! Guilty verdicts will result in headbutts!
201141.touch2: Augh?! C-Commander! Don't you know, crime doesn't pay!

404021.detail: Everyone wants to be a witch for Halloween, so I chose something a little bit different. After seeing your reaction, Commander, I think I chose correctly. Hehehe...
404021.touch: While I haven't prepared any candy, I do have a "treat" for you to enjoy. Would you like to try? I'm afraid there may be some pain involved... Hehehe...
404021.login: At first I was too embarrassed to wear something like this, but I went along with it and after wearing it for a while, I must say I'm starting to see things in a different light...
404021.main: If only my sister were here... Now if we had some sort of pumpkin-smashing gunnery competition, that would have gotten her attention.|This holiday certainly is well suited to us "Ugly Sisters," isn't it?|My tail? Oh it just came with the costume... Still, I'd prefer if you didn't touch it.
404021.unlock: These Halloween festivities are quite interesting, in a good way. Getting dressed up in these costumes isn't such a bad experience either. Commander, what do you think of my costume?
404021.drop_descrip: These Halloween festivities are quite interesting, in a good way. Getting dressed up in these costumes isn't such a bad experience either. Commander, what do you think of my costume?
404021.touch2: Eek?! Commander, does someone want to be "punished?"
404021.home: You say you see ghosts and goblins all around me? ... I think you need a break. Getting into the Halloween spirit is all well and good, but you can't overdo it.

301260.detail: Umm... exactly what do I need to do, to be able to see my sister again?
301260.login: Lord Commander, you’ve worked hard today.
301260.feeling2: Sister {namecode:30} treats me gently, as if I'm her real little sister... but...
301260.mission_complete: It would be great if our rewards can be confirmed as soon as the mission is completed.
301260.main: Rumor has it that we would be able to finish our mission before the pot of tea that we brew got cold? Eh, is this wine? | Even if there is only the slimmest of hope, as long as you persevere, one day you will make it a reality. | Is {namecode:85} coming? She has a mischievous look about her, I’m a little worried.
301260.feeling5: A cool breeze is blowing, the whispers of the wind chimes in the gallery. Feels like a return to summer times with my sister... but, only this time it’s the Lord Commander sitting beside me.
301260.upgrade: If only I could’ve been a little faster, perhaps {namecode:71} sister...
301260.unlock: {namecode:31} class Destroyer {namecode:32}. I am open to your guidance, Lord Commander—— {namecode:30}? No, please do remember I'm {namecode:31} class. This is something I won't back down from!
301260.feeling4: Ahh, it’s the Lord Commander! Eh, no it’s not. I didn’t mean to disappear like that... sorry, my mind simply wandered...
301260.feeling1: Lord Commander, regarding tomorrow’s task— yes, I wish to confirm it all at once...
301260.propose: Lord Commander... before my sister arrives, can I count on you? I can? Thank you... I will take care of the Commander and spend my entire life with you.
301260.skill: For one day when we will eventually reunite...
301260.profile: Second ship of {namecode:31} class Destroyer, {namecode:32}. A lot of people thinks that my sister and I are {namecode:30} class, but they are mistaken. My sister and I participated in many battles in the South Pacific. We helped protect the 4th and 5th Carrier Divisions. We were greatly taken care of by {namecode:98}. This time...I will stay by my sister’s side until the very end.
301260.touch2: Lord Commander, what are you doing!
301260.mission: Let’s brew a pot of tea first before we start our mission.
301260.home: ...Hmm? Is someone there? Sister, is that you? …Sorry, I was dreaming just now...
301260.win_mvp: ...Victory? If only my sister is able to see it...
301260.expedition: The commission is now complete! Lord Commander, would you like to try and build a new ship? Perhaps this time...
301260.mail: Lord Commander, here is your tea, cake and the latest mail.
301260.feeling3: Ahh, it’s the Lord Commander! Why do I have smoke covered all over me? I’m not sure, I was trying to make coke pancakes.
301260.lose: Hmm… I have to bother {namecode:98} again...

107070.detail: Hmm? Commander, you always look at me. Is there something you want to say to me?
107070.touch: I am confident in my own self!
107070.login: Nice weather, Commander. Wanna go somewhere?
107070.feeling2: Eat well, sleep well, play well! Those are my goals~
107070.mission_complete: Hahaha, the mission rewards are here!
107070.main: Commander, if you space out again I'm gonna hit you with a wooden stick~!|Wanna hear about my older sisters? Hmmhmm, now which of them are you smitten by?|Northampton? Well, she's a bit rigid, but she's not a bad girl~
107070.feeling5: You see, I'm not as bothersome as my older sisters. The Hornet you see before you will say that she likes something if she likes it. That's why I'll say this directly: I like you, Commander! How about you?
107070.upgrade: Yeah! Now I'm feeling really great!
107070.unlock: Yo! I'm Hornet! Ah.... I don't want to impose, but don't call me Big Wasp and we'll be fine~ My sisters are both legendary, but just wait and see what I can do!
107070.feeling4: Hey, Commander, are you really not treating me differently because of my sisters? Is that so...? No, I mean, I believe you!
107070.feeling1: Northampton, where are you~? (Hornet doesn't seem to notice you)
107070.propose: Is this your answer, Commander? ... Hehe, umm, well... I'm gonna go outside and run a couple of laps first!
107070.drop_descrip: Yorktown-class aircraft carrier ー Hornet, Hull Number CV-8!
107070.skill: Let's finish this in a jiffy!
107070.profile: I am the Yorktown class' youngest, Hornet! Hmm? Yep, Northampton is my friend! But I don't get what she's thinking. I'm not like my sisters, but I'm strong as well!
107070.mission: Nice weather~ It's a fine day for missions, Commander!
107070.home: Commander, you were awesome back there~!
107070.expedition: Commander, I'm a little sleepy~ Eh, comissions? Ah, that's right! Ehehe, let's go welcome them back, shall we?
couple_encourage: Hey, aren't you bored? Let's get out of here.
I won't be pulled down this time!
Just a few? Don't worry about them~
107070.mail: Secret technique - Doolittle Style Mail Delivery!
107070.feeling3: I'm a twintailed blonde but not a tsundere? Well sorry about that! That's because I, Hornet, am not a stereotypocal woman!
107070.lose: Will I meet a new me?

404020.detail: My duty is to support my big sister who is always charging too far ahead. Admittedly, it gets a little irritating at times.
404020.touch: Isn't it amazing how different people can come to different conclusions about the same topic?
404020.login: Welcome back. Ready to get back to work? I've prepared everything you need, Commander.
404020.battle: Truth only exists within the guns' range.
404020.hp_warning: All ships, remember to stay alert!
404020.feeling2: Is it urgent? I prefer simple and effective forms of communication.
404020.mission_complete: Rewards distributed. Please accept them when you have a moment.
404020.main: You mustn't put off until tomorrow what you can do today. Please take that to heart.|One forgets the cruelty of war after being at peace for too long. The opposite... is true as well, isn't it?|Looking back at it, it's unbelievable that I would mistake that prideful princess as an old-fashioned knight.
404020.feeling5: The present flies by like an arrow, but the future always arrives too late. I hope that one day, I will be able to see the future that you and I create.
404020.upgrade: It's fine as long as you haven't let power cloud your judgement...
404020.unlock: Hello, Commander, I'm Gneisenau. Though my big sister is a bit reckless, we're actually an invincible team. I hope I will be able to sail with her as often as possible!
404020.feeling4: Without realizing it, I've come to enjoy supporting both my sister and you, Commander.
404020.feeling1: I assumed you were more intelligent, Commander...
404020.propose: A promise, huh? Long ago, I would have despised the notion of being tied down to emotions... but it doesn't seem so bad now.
404020.profile: I'm Gneisenau. Though I'm not as bellicose as my sister, I'm still confident about my combat capabilities. As some of the best ships the Iron Blood has to offer, we hold the record of being the only battlecruisers to sink a standard aircraft carrier. Your faith in us will not be misplaced.
404020.touch2: Commander, Anton is locked on, you can't escape now.
404020.mission: A mission? Let me do some planning for you...
404020.home: Welcome back. Please take it easy for a while.
404020.win_mvp: Sorry, this is war. There's no room for mercy.
404020.expedition: A commission has been completed! Care to inspect the results?
404020.mail: Commander, there's mail for you. I'll leave it here.
404020.feeling3: "The Ugly Sisters..." Though we were given that epithet for our achievements, it still hurts a little. Commander, do you think I'm ugly?

401260.detail: I hate snowstorms. One was the reason I got separated from my allies and captured by the enemy...
401260.touch: If you need assistance, just give me the order! ...Err, I mean, please let me know!
401260.login: Sorry, but only authorized personnel are allowed into the office... Oh, I guess you're authorized to enter. Welcome back! Let's give it our all!
401260.battle: All ships, follow the vanguard's lead! Oh, I guess that means follow me!
401260.hp_warning: I wonder where Z25 and the others went...
401260.feeling2: What I do when a foe's aiming at me? Well... I pray that they fire at someone else by accident! If they don't, I pray again that their torpedoes don't hit me!
401260.mission_complete: A mission has been completed! If Zed were here, she'd say... "Commander, you've done well!"
401260.main: Commander, slacking off is absolutely prohibited! ...You've already finished your work? I-in that case... Well done!|Zed's good at studying, and Lebe's good at sports... so I should aim to... study while playing sports? W-will I manage?|I wonder if Z25's Mr. Anchor is actually alive... I mean, she's always talking to it, so...
401260.feeling5: Commander! I was observing your work, and it looks like you can do just fine without my supervision! What a good job you've done. You're stellar! I'm very proud of you.
401260.upgrade: I'm very grabbed! ...No, I mean, I'm very grateful!
401260.unlock: I'm the Iron Blood destroyer, Z26! I look forward to working with you! ...All right, that should do just fine as an introduction...!
401260.feeling4: Maintaining a good work-life balance is very important! That's why I'll be watching you on your days off to make sure you don't do any work! This is me telling you to get enough rest.
401260.propose: "I take you, to have and to hold, from this day forward, for better, for worse, for richer, for poorer, in sickness and in health, until death do us part." ...I was able to recite it from memory! Now it's your turn... right?
401260.profile: So you want to hear about my history? Absolutely! As the Iron Blood Type 1936A destroyer, Z26, I escorted Hipper and Scheer, and disrupted shipping with Z25 and the others. While doing so, I was defeated... and that's that!
401260.touch2: No lewdness allowed! Ever! Full stop!
401260.mission: New damn missions have co– Err, I mean! Commander, please hurry up and check out the new missions!
401260.home: Commander, here's some coffee! ...S-sugar? Hmm... I wonder if 10 cubes will be enough...
401260.win_mvp: Continue making your best endeavors! ...Um, I mean, well done, everyone!
401260.expedition: The commission team is back! They've really done it this time... Nono, I mean, they've done a good job!
couple_encourage: Please don't stray too far from me!
401260.mail: Here's the latest intel! Please give it a look, Commander!
401260.feeling3: Commander, you did a great job, like always! Continue to do your best tomorrow as well! ...You can tell that I'm complimenting you right now, no?
401260.lose: We ended up losing... I'm really sorry, everyone!

401261.detail: Spee really likes these bugle crunches a whole lot. Do you like them too, Commander? Then, open up, I'll chuck a few in for you!
401261.touch: Press this button to start a new game! ...Um, Commander, weren't you asking about where the start button is?
401261.login: Sorry to keep you waiting! These are all my belongings! ...I mean, uhh, these are all my snacks and games!
401261.main: U96 pwned me again! Maybe I should practice more with Ryuujou before challenging her... Oh, Commander, I'm talking about a fighting game I've been playing with U96 and the others! |If you're tired, you should try hugging Sharky and taking a nap! ...Ah, I meant that Sharky pillow on the bed!|My sisters are always telling me not to spend too much time gaming. But since it's my day off, does it reallly matter how much I play?
401261.unlock: Commander, welcome to my pad! Ah, give me a sec, let me go grab all the snacks and drinks and games!
401261.drop_descrip: Commander, welcome to my pad! Ah, give me a sec, let me go grab all the snacks and drinks and games!
401261.home: You thirsty, Commander? I've got Cola, milk, and even the fizzy stuff Hipper and Eugen drink when they come over to play. They're all in that mini-fridge over there, so take whatever you want!

101253.detail: Stop staring at me already, stupid Commander! ...You need to, or you can't evaluate my dancing? Well... stop staring anyway!
101253.touch: You want me to shake fans' hands? With these bulky paws?
101253.battle: I-I'm going into battle wearing THIS?!
101253.mission_complete: Here, the rewards. That Chesh-something girl came and delivered it earlier.
101253.main: This attachable tail can move? Really, huh... And why do you know that?!|Hah, aren't these cat ears just the cutest? I thought so.|Eldridge's costume looks easier to move about in... N-no, I don't wanna try it, you stupid perv!
101253.unlock: Ughh... These gloves are so heavy and the dress is too revealing. Why on earth did I decide to put these on... I can't show myself to Yorktown like this!
101253.drop_descrip: Ughh... These gloves are so heavy and the dress is too revealing. Why on earth did I decide to put these on... I can't show myself to Yorktown like this!
101253.mission: Go review our job offers! Now!
101253.home: Well done and all that... Wait, what do you mean "Sims took pictures?!" Why didn't you tell me that sooner?!
101253.win_mvp: Hmph! That's what happens when you poke fun at me!
101253.expedition: Hey, dummy, commission complete... No! There's no way in hell I'm going out wearing this!
101253.lose: Dang it... I told you I can't fight like this!

406011.detail: Sit down and relax. Have some rich tea, or read a nice book to ease off.
406011.touch: Oh, we're going to a Sakura Empire shrine for New Year's? Heheh. I'm looking forward to the memories we'll make today.
406011.login: Have you already decided what we'll do today? If not, take your time. The goddess of time is a patient one.
406011.main: The Sakura Empire's New Year's banquet? I'd love to go, but... Eugen, can you promise you won't get drunk out of your mind again?|Cozy winter sunsets really make you drowsy... I just take a short nap... Zzz...|On New Year's Eve, you're meant to put work on hold, relax, and take in the start of a new year. You should do exactly that, Commander.
406011.unlock: I've been waiting for you, Comander. As per my sister's recommendation, I've put on this Sakura Empire kimono. It was very tricky to get into, I might add... That aside, how do I look? ...Good enough, I hope?
406011.drop_descrip: I've been waiting for you, Comander. As per my sister's recommendation, I've put on this Sakura Empire kimono. It was very tricky to get into, I might add... That aside, how do I look? ...Good enough, I hope?
406011.touch2: Okay, you've proven just how tenacious you are. Now, could you stop it already?
406011.home: Welcome back. Give me a moment to put in a bookmark.

402039.detail: Data aside, if there's anything else you'd like to know, please don't hesitate to ask.
402039.touch: Don't you have more important things to be doing than staring at me or chatting with me?
402039.login: Today's task list. I've taken the liberty of sorting them in order of priority. Please review them.
402039.main: Detailed planning ensured the efficient completion of one's work. Commander, next on the list is――|Such desk work demands a quiet and peaceful atmosphere. Well, I suppose that means I should hope my sisters don't come barging in...|Commander, what would you say to coming by the Tactical Classroom to observe some lessons in your free time?
402039.unlock: Hmm... I feel like I can work even more efficiently than before. Commander, please rest assured, I will never betray your expectations.
402039.drop_descrip: Hmm... I feel like I can work even more efficiently than before. Commander, please rest assured, I will never betray your expectations.
402039.touch2: ...From time to time, one should consider the rumors spreading around the port about oneself, Commander...

202260.detail: Never thought the story would turn out like this! Cannot wait for next week's issue... Huh?! M-Master! Ahem! How may I help you?
202260.login: Welcome back, Master. I've prepared tea.
202260.battle: Flagship... is it? I, I can do this!
202260.feeling2: You should rest if you're feeling tired... Th-think about those of us working for you.
202260.mission_complete: The rewards are here. I'll put 'em away for ye.
202260.main: Newcastle, ye ask? She's like a big sister and that's all I have to say to you... nothing else!|Sheffy's got a sharp tongue, but really she's a sweet lassie.|You wouldn't happen to like manga or...? N-never mind. Forget I asked.
202260.feeling5: I made your bed, warmed your sheets, and ye ended up working all night anyway... Oh no, I'm not mad in the slightest. Hard work is to be praised, after all~
202260.upgrade: Aye. I shall redouble my efforts.
202260.unlock: I'm Glasgow, light cruiser part of the Southampton subclass of the Town class. I am honoured to be part of your fleet, Commander. I am at your service.
202260.feeling4: You'd like to see me in my casual attire? D-didn't you say I'd look cute in anything? I'll leave it to your imagination then~
202260.feeling1: Would you please be so kind as to maintain a distance of at least three metres from my person so that I may properly carry out my duties as a maid, "Master?"
202260.propose: And so I thank God for bestowing upon me the gift of our meeting... And we're done, eh? Time to go home...? Huh? S-seal the vow with a k-kiss?! B-but... I...!
202260.profile: I'm Glasgow, Southampton-class light cruiser of the Royal Navy. I fought in the Norwegian Campaign, escorted our ships through the Arctic, and participated in various other operations... B- but my eyes aren't that great. I oughta apologise to Imogen...
202260.mission: A new mission is here. Please check it soon.
202260.home: That'll do. Take a rest now.
202260.win_mvp: Phew... That'd be enough for ye now, eh?
202260.expedition: The commission fleet has returned. Please remember to welcome them back.
couple_encourage: For the glory of the Royal Navy! Commence the attack!
Ever thought about rejoining the Maids?
202260.mail: Looks like we got new mail. I'll grab it.
202260.feeling3: Master, I've brought you a change of fresh white linens... You'd prefer green, like the color of my eyes? I, I see...
202260.lose: Have to think on that one... Don't wanna lose again.

205100.detail: Look, isn't Elizabeth acting a bit too spoiled? And Warspite and the others are totally enabling that. I knew I should have been the one in charge... Huhh? I'm more or less the same...? Wh-what did you say?!
205100.touch: Speak your mind, my attendant. You have my ear.
205100.login: It's about time! Now, show me today's itinerary!
205100.hp_warning: H-hey, hurry up and do something about this...!
205100.feeling2: Good, you came. If you have no other work to do, play me in a game of chess.
205100.mission_complete: Even the most trivial quests at least deserve some rewards.
205100.main: So thirsty... Ahem. My attendant, do tell the Maid Team to brew me some black tea. Hmm, on second thought... that'd take too long. You can do it for me, can't you?|Charisma is the most important facet of a leader! To be charismatic is to command dignity, to imbue your every word with gravitas! Ahem... did you get all that?|Snack time?! ...Ahem! A proper leader must know how to balance their work with their life. Please do not forget that.
205100.feeling5: As my subordinate, you should be considerate of your superior... I mean, sh-shouldn't you let me win at least once? I've lost to you so many times that I barely even have the confidence to play chess anymore... A-anyway! Lose to me! Just once! It can even be on purpose! This is an order, got it?
205100.upgrade: Not bad, my attendant~ Do you want a reward?
205100.unlock: To be Valiant is to be me. Remember this face, for it is the face of a fleet leader! ...Speaking of faces, who are you? The Commander? Very well! I shall treat you as my personal servant!
205100.feeling4: H-hold up! Chess is like a real-world exercise, so you have to consider all the various external factors! Th-that's right! That last match was a fake! A fluke! Doesn't count! Cancelled! Got it?!
205100.feeling1: I had great expectations for you...
205100.propose: Well done! You've gained my recognition as my trustiest spear in the arsenal! To reward you for your continued loyalty, I shall allow you to stay at my side and bask in my charisma! May this ring be a symbol of our bond~♪
205100.skill: Everything dances within the palm of my hand!
205100.profile: Queen Elizabeth-class battleship, Valiant. Hehe, this fleet is known from Jutland to the Far East for its heroic majesty, and I am the reason for that! Now, Commander, you shall become my assistant so that you may prove your worth as a subordinate.
205100.touch2: What's the meaning of this?! Grrr... As a charismatic, generous, and VERY patient person, I will forgive you just this once!
205100.mission: I'll leave this these trifling quests to you.
205100.home: My attendant, how fares the combat situation? Do tell me in detail.
205100.win_mvp: A heroic battle commanded elegantly by the Commander— now this is the kind of flawless victory that befits me.
205100.expedition: Heheh, it seems that the commission team has been doing well. Do send them my best regards in my stead.
couple_encourage: Feast your eyes upon the might of the noble Queen Elizabeth-class!
M-make sure you observe my every move!
205100.mail: Tsk... Why is all the mail for you...
205100.feeling3: Y-you're better than I expected... F-fine, I won't go easy on you next time...!

406010.detail: Commander, are you free? Do you have time to help me practice with my planes?
406010.touch: If you're tired, just set everything else aside and get some rest. I'll wake you up if somebody comes around.
406010.login: Before you hurry off to do your work, why not first take a seat and enjoy a cup of coffee?
406010.battle: Keep calm and persevere. Victory will surely come to us.
406010.hp_warning: It's not yet time to panic.
406010.feeling2: The battlefield is a place where the unexpected occurs. If you simply insist on following the orders given to you by the higher-ups, you'll never be able to achieve victory.
406010.mission_complete: Mission complete. Don't worry, it's not like the rewards will run off somewhere. You just need to make sure to collect them later.
406010.main: The Iron Blood doesn't have as many aircraft carriers as the other factions, so I can't help but worry that we'll be at a disadvantage during practice exercises.|The Unsinkable Battleship...? Oh, I know who you're talking about. I wonder if I'll ever be able to meet my renowned predecessor, Seydlitz, at some point?|Hipper, Eugen... I can't believe I'm able to fight by their side like this. It's all thanks to you, Commander.
406010.feeling5: Have you matched your stride to my tempo, or have I matched mine to meet yours? Putting all that aside, you know, having you by my side makes me feel comfortable and relaxed. Hehe.
406010.upgrade: It looks like I'll get to use some more powerful equipment. Thanks, Commander.
406010.unlock: Heavy cruiser, Seydlitz... Rather, escort carrier Weser, has arrived. You're wondering why I have two names? Don't be in such a rush... I'll be sure to teach you later, slowly.
406010.feeling4: I believe that the way we live isn't influenced by our environment, but rather the choices we've made. That's why I've always lived by my own tempo. What do you think about the way I live my life?
406010.feeling1: Commander, I've got one word of advice for you. If your condition isn't great, make sure to take a break and sleep soundly. It won't do to have everyone else see you in bad shape.
406010.propose: This ceremony... Surely you didn't have to be in such a rush? It's not like I'll run off somewhere or forget our promises together. Or... is it that you don't have any faith in me? Hehe, I'm just messing with you. For the future everlasting, I'll be yours, Commander.
406010.profile: Whether as the 4th ship of the Admiral Hipper class, Seydlitz, or as the escort carrier, Weser, I was never completed over the entirety of that war. ...Over here, I should have more than enough time to do everything I've always wanted to do. That way, I'll be able to bury my regrets, one by one.
406010.touch2: Your spirited enthusiasm... You might want to change the way you convey it.
406010.mission: New missions? There's no need to hurry. We can check them after you finish whatever you're doing right now.
406010.home: Being a commander truly takes a surprising amount of work... How about taking a quick breather right about now?
406010.expedition: The commissions team is back? We shouldn't leave them waiting there like that... Should I go ahead and greet them first?
couple_encourage: I wonder what your plan might be?
Head forth without worry, we've got you covered.
406010.mail: There's some mail for you. If it's nothing urgent, just read them later.
406010.feeling3: Peter is quite brilliant, but she can also be quite dreary. I wish she'd loosen up about time and planning and all, and learn to just have fun sometimes.
406010.lose: Ugh... I wonder if I'm still not used to my planes...

499028.detail: What I hope to get from you? Hehe... For me, the most important thing in the world... what I hope for the most - is you, my child.
499028.touch: Do you wish to touch your beloved more intimately? Come closer, my dear child.
499028.login: What would you like to listen to today, my child?
499028.main: Is there something giving you difficulty? Please tell me about it. I shall take care of everything for you.|Save your cold rationality for your enemies on the battlefield. Before me, however, you need not hold back. Just indulge yourself to your heart's desire, my child.|If you are tired, lie down right here... I will bring you pleasant dreams... Good, sweet child... I'll always be watching over you.
499028.feeling5: My child, I will accept you unconditionally, and lay low anything that attempts to stand in your way. Come, allow me to pamper you more. Yes, more... more... give me more...
499028.unlock: Ahh, the dreamlike beauty of this variation... let us write down this movement so that it may continue forever, my sweet child.
499028.drop_descrip: Ahh, the dreamlike beauty of this variation... let us write down this movement so that it may continue forever, my sweet child.
499028.touch2: What a selfish child... But no matter, I shall accept you unconditionally.
499028.home: You can leave the report for later. Let me see your face, my child... Hehe, there's nothing amiss... Is there anything you'd like to talk to me about, my child?

202121.detail: The outfits of the Dragon Empery do have a certain charm. Perhaps I can give them a little recommendation to the rest of the maid team. What do you think?
202121.touch: Despite the fact that it is a holiday, I am still ready to sortie.
202121.login: Welcome back, Master. I specially procured some different teas from the Dragon Empery. Which one would you like to try first?
202121.main: A variety of culinary techniques and seasoning methods... the food culture of the Dragon Empery is truly eye-opening. |It's customary in the Dragon Empery for everyone to get together on New Year's to have a banquet? Ahh, so many people to serve... my maid's soul is trembling! |Only a few girls from the Dragon Empery have joined our fleet. Because of that, I can't afford to let them feel lonely.
202121.feeling5: Did you know, Master... all I can do for you is to learn from the cultures of the other camps in order to provide you with better service. But all this pales in comparison to all that you do for us on a daily basis, yet you take yourself for granted... What a lovable but also hateable person.
202121.unlock: Hehe... Master, why are you so stunned from seeing me? I thought you perhaps wanted to see me in a qipao... was I mistaken?
202121.drop_descrip: Hehe... Master, why are you so stunned from seeing me? I thought you perhaps wanted to see me in a qipao... was I mistaken?
202121.touch2: I see, Master. The biggest drawback of this qipao is its ability to rob you of your self-control.
202121.home: I baked this pastry for a certain Master who is so absorbed in work to the point of forgetting to eat. Please enjoy it.
202121.expedition: Master, what do you think about handing some red envelopes to the hardworking girls still out on commissions?

302010.detail: Be they canisters or weaponry, my developments in them are the latest!
302010.touch: Your hand is so warm and gentle, Master~
302010.login: With you by my side, Master, I have nothing to fear...!
302010.battle: Combat trial for new equipment... begin!
302010.hp_warning: Oww... No issue, as long as my equipment is fine...
302010.feeling2: Master, what's on your mind when you stare at me? Hohoho, I'm rather perceptive, I'll have you know!
302010.mission_complete: Master, I believe it is time for a nap once you've finished your missions.
302010.main: *Yawn*...|Melon bread? I'm extraordinarily curious as to how it tastes...|The Gatos are terrifying... Why are such frightening submarines named after a catshark?
302010.feeling5: Do you want to nap with me, Master? Take this, it is my favorite pillow. Perhaps if you sleep on it, you will see me in your dreams. And if you do... Hehehe♪
302010.upgrade: Hmm... It seems to be a bit too tight in here...
302010.unlock: I am light cruiser Yuubari. You say we've met before, Master? Hmm... b-but that's not possible... I don't have any sisters after all...
302010.feeling4: What girls are your type, Master? Someone like me? You know, my type is people like you, Master~
302010.feeling1: Master, could you just stay away from me?
302010.propose: I'm overjoyed♪ Starting today, every day when you wake up, the first thing you'll see in the morning is me~! Hehehe♪
302010.skill: Feel the power of my advanced weapons!
302010.profile: I am Yuubari, Sakura Empire Yuubari-class light cruiser. I was developed under the constraints of a naval treaty, but this conversely allowed me to utilize a great number of new technologies. I served as the flagship of a Destroyer Squadron in the Pacific War. Hmm... I will need many oxygen torpedoes if I am to research them...
302010.touch2: Mmh... ugh... gah... stop, or I will bite!
302010.mission: You have incomplete missions... Hmm, it appears the results of my research will not be of any use...
302010.home: Data collection complete. Now we shall use it to improve our gear.
302010.win_mvp: Surely by now, you've begun to understand the importance of developing new gear, Master?
302010.expedition: A commission is done! Hmm, I wonder if they brought us gifts...
302010.mail: Hmm, this mail seems questionable... Master, I urge you to open it!
302010.feeling3: I much prefer staying in the port than going on sorties. This is my home; by the blue seas, beneath the warm and dazzling sunlight... *Yawn*... Mmhh... Zzzz...
302010.lose: Dear me! ... Once I'm done developing new gear, I won't lose like this again!

202261.detail: Enterprise? I know her. We fought together at the Bay of Biscay, eh? Huh? There's another Enterprise...? I-I knew that!
202261.touch: Ye want ta watch me doing my club work? Um, well, ye could say I'm in the "Go Home Club..."
202261.login: Good to see you back. I've only just got home from school meself. Oh... erm... the tea... just a moment.
202261.main: What's for lunch? How's this lunchbox here sound to ye? Just a little something I made meself...|That Z23 from the Iron Blood's got a talent for teaching. Teacher or no. Not that I need the help.|Borrowed this one from Ranger. Gotta finish it soon. It's the sequel to a story I've been waiting for.
202261.unlock: Y-ye said ye wanted ta see me wear something different, so... But this is not "cosplay" or somesuch! I do actually go to school...! D-do ye like it?
202261.drop_descrip: Y-ye said ye wanted ta see me wear something different, so... But this is not "cosplay" or somesuch! I do actually go to school...! D-do ye like it?
202261.expedition: Commission team's back. I'll go get 'em.

406012.detail: This dress took just about forever to pick out. Judging from your reaction though, I can see that it wasn't time wasted, hehe.
406012.touch: Are you getting bored? Want to head out to enjoy the breeze together?
406012.login: There's still plenty of time until the party ends. If there's anything you wanted to do with me, then go ahead, Commander.
406012.main: Even though we've toasted over so many drinks already, I can't believe that you're still so lively. I might have underestimated you a bit, Commander.|As my lovely knight in shining armor, Commander, don't you think you should be asking your princess for a dance?|The girls of the Iron Blood are calling for me. Come greet them with me, Commander.
406012.unlock: Ah, I've kept you waiting. I do apologize that it took so long to get changed into this outfit. Now, Commander, won't you come show me your chivalry and escort me down these stairs?
406012.drop_descrip: Ah, I've kept you waiting. I do apologize that it took so long to get changed into this outfit. Now, Commander, won't you come show me your chivalry and escort me down these stairs?
406012.touch2: That is not a chivalrous way to conduct yourself.
406012.home: How about doing something else for a change of pace? Just let me know if you want to spend some time together, whether it's inside the banquet hall or outside.

401234.detail: I've been smiling a lot more lately? ... Well, that's because you've gotten so much more respectable.
401234.touch: D-D-Dance?! ... Oh my, I never thought it might come to this... Commander, can you teach me how to do it...?
401234.login: Are you enjoying the party, Commander?
401234.mission_complete: This is... exactly what I'd expect from my Commander.
401234.main: When I see everyone's smiling faces, I can't help but think about all the hard work that got us here. How about you, Commander?|The four of us: Laffey, Javelin, Ayanami, and I... Who would have thought we'd all become such good friends?|Champagne? Oh, heavens no, Commander! This is just sparkling orange juice.
401234.feeling5: Erm, well, Commander! I don't usually think about things like this but, you know, tonight, I'm wondering, Commander, when I'm all dressed up like this, do you think I'm... well... pretty?
401234.unlock: Oh, good evening, Commander. I was just looking for Javelin and the others... Say, would you like to keep me company for a bit?
401234.drop_descrip: Oh, good evening, Commander. I was just looking for Javelin and the others... Say, would you like to keep me company for a bit?
401234.mission: Just for today, Commander, I don't mind you putting off your missions for a while.
401234.home: Commander, you don't mind if I cut a bit loose today, do you?
401234.mail: Look how many invitations you've gotten, Commander. Aren't you popular? Hehehe.
401234.lose: What can I do? ... I don't want to get my dress dirty.

103100.detail: Wanna space out and stare at the clouds?
103100.touch: Commander... can you guess what I'm thinking right now?
103100.hp_warning: I... I can still keep fighting! Probably...
103100.feeling2: Quincy is always busy helping other people, so she never has time to space out with me...
103100.mission_complete: Commander, why don't you let me take a nap as a reward instead...?
