Also, it helps that I'm not the lead vocalist, hehe. |Montpelier, Denver, what the heck are you wearing? That's embarrassing...! And Birmingham, you don't have to go waving that thing around!
102240.feeling5: Whew... You've really helped me out tons, Commander... I'm not the greatest when it comes to this stuff, and I never thought I could be a star on stage like you've made me... We really were meant to be together, Commander!
102240.upgrade: All those lessons are paying off!
102240.unlock: Light cruiser Cleveland, right here! I'm new to this whole idol biz, but I'll go with the flow and give it my all! Oh, and I'm counting on your support, Commander!
102240.feeling4: Dammit, Columbia... She's an expert at this stuff so I asked her to help. I'm shocked she wrote a bio for me that's half lies... Thank goodness you fixed it, Commander, or else I would've died of shame on stage...
102240.feeling1: Sorry, I've got more important stuff to do. I don't have time for you.
102240.propose: I heard that in some places, idols aren't allowed to be in relationships. Well, I'm sure we'll be fine! Anyway, Commander... Hehe, please continue to take good care of me!
102240.drop_descrip: Light cruiser Cleveland, right here! I'm new to this whole idol biz, but I'll go with the flow and give it my all! Oh, and I'm counting on your support, Commander!
102240.profile: I'm Cleveland, the light cruiser. My sisters and I took part in the World War and... Well, let's just say we did pretty good for ourselves. This time around I'm wearing this special uniform, and I'm gonna fight with the power of song!
102240.touch2: Commander?! I'm trying to get by as an idol here! Th-Think of my image...
102240.mission: We've got job offers... I mean, commissions! Let's get 'em done!
102240.home: Oh, you tired? The dressing room is free right now. You could use that if it's too exhausting to walk to the office.
102240.win_mvp: Whew! So who's our next target?
102240.expedition: Commission complete! Don't forget everyone's got a schedule to follow, all right?
102240.mail: New mail's come in! I've already told you: it's for you, not for me! Come on already!
102240.feeling3: Maybe saying I grow bonsai as a hobby sounds too basic... Maybe it is... Gah, I'm at my wit's end! Commander, what do I write to make a decent self-introduction?
102240.lose: I can't show myself to my sisters like this...

201270.detail: Is it fun to hang out with me, Commander? ...Ah, sorry, never mind that.
201270.touch: Hehehe~! You've reloaded me with energy!
201270.login: Morning, Commander! Nice weather today! Click, click... bang! I'm not sure why, but I'm always brimming with energy!
201270.feeling2: No matter what life throws at you, always be optimistic, happy, and positive! You just gotta be!
201270.mission_complete: Hehehe~ It's just human instinct to smile at the sight of money! Yeah, that's it! Smile, Commander~!
201270.main: Something nice is gonna happen today~ That's what I'm feeling!|Why am I always smiling? Hehehe, because I've been having so much fun ever since I came here!|The injuries I've sustained from combat? Hehehe, they don't hurt at all.
201270.feeling5: So much has happened since we first met... But I haven't changed a bit!
201270.unlock: I am the M-class Destroyer, Musketeer! Hehe... I knew something good was going to happen today~ Commander, can you point me to where the port is? Here? Or over here?!
201270.feeling4: We should all forget our worries and live to have fun! Don't you think so too, Commander?
201270.feeling1: Come on... Return to your former self, Commander...
201270.propose: Thank you, Commander! This is the best thing I've ever gotten! Hey, tell me: have I given you some good memories, too?
201270.skill: Locked and loaded~! Ready to fire!
201270.profile: I'm the Royal Navy M-class destroyer Musketeer! I was in the Battle of the North Cape! Commander, little Musketeer is gonna shoot straight through your dreary heart with a bang bang!
201270.touch2: It's not like I *dislike* it, but... Yeah, I actually don't dislike it!
201270.mission: Finish them all in one go!
201270.home: Take a gander at my new marching act, Commander! Relax, I'm only using blanks this time!
201270.win_mvp: I'm gonna punch a hole straight through your heart~! Heheh, I've always wanted to say that!
201270.expedition: Wooow! Look at those mission rewards! We could fill a bathtub with all this oil!
201270.mail: Heehee~! See? I told you something nice would happen today!
201270.feeling3: I always have tons of fun hanging out with you!
201270.lose: Time to make a sneaky exit~♫

205101.detail: Hey you, don't tell me you're actually enjoying being taken care of like this?! Grr... How unfair! How about this, next time, I'll be the patient, and you'll attend to my every whim!
205101.touch: What's the matter? Are you going to die if I don't take care of you~?
205101.login: It's about time! ...Wait, just kidding! You're supposed to be the patient, right? How about you stop walking around so much? Get back in bed this instant!
205101.main: Don't get any weird ideas. I'm only pouring tea for you because you're the patient!|When we're not training for this exercise, how about a game of chess? I already brought the board. I'll set it up, so just wait in bed!|As a patient, so you're supposed to listen to the nurse! Mm... Besides, shouldn't you already be heeding my every instruction? You're my attendant after all...|You're my patient today! Heheh, be grateful that you're now under the care of the charismatic nurse, Valiant, and heed my every command! ...It, it's not like I'm into this or anything, so don't expect me to do this every single time!|It's time to get your blood drawn, so stick your arm out! ...Geh... I can't handle this stuff like Vampire does...
205101.unlock: Hehe~ As this medical facility training is crucially important, a charismatic leader such as myself would be best suited to instruct everyone on– Wait a moment, what's with this outfit?! You there, explain the meaning of this at once!
205101.drop_descrip: Hehe~ As this medical facility training is crucially important, a charismatic leader such as myself would be best suited to instruct everyone on– Wait a moment, what's with this outfit?! You there, explain the meaning of this at once!
205101.touch2: ...I, I'm only overlooking this because you're the patient!
205101.home: I brought water for you. Make sure you drink plenty if you want to stay healthy... That's right, eight cups a day!

401238.detail: Commander, I can't concentrate on my reading if you're staring at me like that! Gosh...
401238.touch: Yes, yes, I know I look cute in this outfit, so hurry up and get back to work! Jeez, what am I to do with you, Commander...
401238.login: Commander, did you make sure to eat the meal I made for you? Mmhmm, good, good~
401238.main: Commander, I'll be here reading, so just call my name if something happens. I have to study hard so that I can keep up with you!|You look so cool and hardworking like that... Uh, ahem! Disregard that! A-anyway, would you like a light snack?|How to help the Commander work more efficiently and comfortably... Hmm, it'll be quite the challenge, but well worth it!
401238.feeling5: Commander, no matter what destination you're aiming for, I'll be with you every step of the way, whether you're at the summit or just setting out, through both joys and disappointments. Mhm, you'll never be alone again, I swear it.
401238.unlock: Whew... Sorry to keep you waiting. I was having a hard time deciding which outfit to wear... Ah, um... how do I look?
401238.drop_descrip: Whew... Sorry to keep you waiting. I was having a hard time deciding which outfit to wear... Ah, um... how do I look?
401238.touch2: Wait, if you're going to do this kind of stuff, at least save it for after work! Even if I like... I mean, err, d-disregard what I just said!
401238.home: Mm... there really was a lot to consider on that last operation... but most importantly, I'm glad you're safe, Commander.
401238.win_mvp: Instructor, how many points did my combat performance score? ...Heheh, just kidding~
401238.lose: I-I'm all right... but I'll have to train more after we get back...

103101.detail: I like dreaming. There are no missions... or fighting... or sorrows...
103101.touch: Astoria... don't shake me please... Zzz...
103101.main: In my dreams, everyone can play together happily... |Zzz... the donut monster... is gonna catch me... zzz... |Mr. Meowy got so big... zzz...
103101.touch2: Zzz... Ahh... donut monster... not right there... Commander, save meee... zzz....

106010.detail: Can't see me... can't see me... can't see me...
106010.touch: Commander, you dummy~! There's glue here~! ...Wh-What?! I'm stuck?! What do I do?!
106010.login: Roooaar! ... Hehehe, were you shocked? I'm like a ghost that's going to haunt you every day!
106010.battle: Ehehe, let's party~ I'm gonna scare you to the point you're spilling fuel!
106010.mission_complete: Sneaky... sneaky... Apply glue to Commander's rewards...
106010.main: Russian roulette~ candy time~ Pick the one~ with wasabi inside~|Let's drink together, eh? Cheeers~ Bfft! So bitter... I ended up drinking what the Commander is supposed to drink!|Commander~ Do my sleeves~ look like those of a ghost~?
106010.feeling5: That said, if I am really a ghost possessing Commander, I would have to be with you all the time. During meals, during naps, when going to the bathr... Wha! Too embarrassing!
106010.upgrade: Long Island's... EXP points... have been increased!
106010.unlock: Hehe, I'm Long Island~ Hello, Commander. Actually, I have another name. Do you want to know?
106010.feeling4: Hehehe, Long Island the ghost has 'accidentally' possessed Commander, and cannot leave ever again~ Now Commander has no choice but to spend his every day life like this!
106010.feeling1: Commander... He can't see me... He can't see me...
106010.propose: Contract established~! With this, Long Island has officially become the ghost possessing Commander~! ...But what I do will not change... Ehehe~
106010.drop_descrip: Long Island-class escort carrier – Long Island, Hull Number CVE-1!
106010.profile: Hehehe, I am Long Island. Eagle Union's first escort carrier~ Using cute little planes to protect merchant ships, as well as sea lanes... That is my job~
106010.touch2: Wh- what you touched isn't me! What you touched... is...a... a ghost!
106010.mission: Commander~ there's a new mission~ Once you are done~ let's sleep?
106010.home: Com~man~der~ No one has returned yet~
106010.win_mvp: Hehehe~ Look at them! They don't even know what hit them!
106010.expedition: The girls who went out on commission aren't back yet~ Not yet~ ...Ah, they're back now!
couple_encourage: This ghost can pwn any of you in video games!
106010.mail: Long Island used [Switcheroo] on Commander's mail! I am amazing!
106010.feeling3: The right answer is... BOO! Hahahahaah I Scared you! ... Ehhh... Commander, you suck at playing along...
106010.lose: No... No way... Could they possibly have seen me?!

202124.detail: Master, what would you like for lunch? I prepared some... Hmm? You're fine with just that? Master, you can't have snacks as a meal.
202124.touch: Holding hands? ... Master, there's something nostalgic about this feeling.
202124.login: I am accustomed to being the one who makes the arrangements, but occasionally letting others make plans for me has merits of its own. Master, our next location is for you to decide. Hehe~ I'm looking forward to it.
202124.main: This snack seems to be quite popular these days. Master, would you like some? Here, say "ahhn~" Hehe, so this must be a part of the reason why it's popular. |As a maid, it is my duty to serve you. However, so that you may leave a positive impression of yourself upon others, I will entrust the duty of carrying these bags to you, Master. |I should pick out some outfits for the other maids as well, not just for me... Of course, I'll be doing the same for you, Master. Hehe~
202124.unlock: Hehe~ Judging from your expression, Master, my outfit has not fallen short of your expectations. As time is precious, allow me to serve you to the utmost on this "date."
202124.drop_descrip: Hehe~ Judging from your expression, Master, my outfit has not fallen short of your expectations. As time is precious, allow me to serve you to the utmost on this "date."
202124.touch2: Even on a date, one ought not be too impatient. Understood, Master?
202124.home: Master, if you don't know where you'd like to go next, why don't we just wander around for a while? Sometimes, the most serendipitous sights are the most memorable of all.

401239.detail: Ok, just little bit more and the retrofit will be complete... let’s go find Javelin and play with them—— Hey, *points*, it’s the Commander?! *Cough*, great timing, here are some documents...
401239.login: Commander, look alive, let’s make a greater effort on our attacks.
401239.main: nil|nil|| Once we complete today’s mission, then come back and confirm our schedule for sorties over the next few days, there are still many things left to do.
401239.unlock: My efficiency should be upgraded along with my performance. Paperwork, battle plans... I can handle them all! Commander, be prepared, we’ll be very busy~
401239.drop_descrip: My efficiency should be upgraded along with my performance. Paperwork, battle plans... I can handle them all! Commander, be prepared, we’ll be very busy~
401239.touch2: Commander, are you prepared to work in a lockdown environment?
401239.win_mvp: Well done, let’s keep this up, everyone!

199021.detail: My dress? Oh, Seattle helped me with it. We all know I couldn't get it looking like this myself...
199021.touch: Woah!! That was close... Thanks, Commander. Getting around in high heels isn't exactly my forte.
199021.login: It's so much easier to relax when we're alone... Don't you think, Commander?
199021.main: Whew, now this is a fine place to enjoy a cola. You want one, Commander? I brought extra.|Don't you have to hurry back to the party, Commander? Lots of girls waiting for you, no?|Don't worry about it, Commander. I love the fleet. I'll head back inside in a bit.
199021.feeling5: I love being with you under the moonlight, Commander... Err, not like that. Unless...? I mean, I could maybe mean it like that... Sorry, I'm making it weird... This is so awkward...
199021.unlock: Oh? Commander, did you need to get some fresh air as well? Me? Ahaha... It's a bit too stiff inside that venue, so I came out for a change of pace. Why don't we take a little stroll together?
199021.drop_descrip: Oh? Commander, did you need to get some fresh air as well? Me? Ahaha... It's a bit too stiff inside that venue, so I came out for a change of pace. Why don't we take a little stroll together?
199021.home: Commander, the air out here is delightful. Come take a breather.

900046.detail: Hehe~ Which do you prefer: matcha, or black tea?
900046.touch: I can take you anywhere the ocean reaches.
900046.login: There is nothing more relaxing than a banquet following a battle... By the way, Commander, I'm free after this...
900046.battle: Hehe, shall we go enjoy the festivities?
900046.hp_warning: Commander... It's too early to give up just yet!
900046.feeling2: Ehehe~ Commander, is there something on your mind?
900046.mission_complete: Hehe, shall we celebrate by holding a banquet tonight?
900046.main: *Sigh*... Whenever Kirishima comes to a banquet, all those kids that tag along with her usually end up making a mess of things... |When it comes to warfare, wisdom and courage are equally important. We can't count on another miracle if we discard proper planning and rely on blind courage. |Commander, I'll be able to protect you, no matter the situation. Hehe, I am called an "Imperial Ship" because I have that capacity after all~♪
900046.feeling5: Commander, after tonight's banquet... will you be free? Hehe, please look forward to it~
900046.upgrade: Today's breeze feels more pleasant than usual.
900046.unlock: I am the Imperial Ship Hiei, second of the Kongou-class, reporting for duty. Commander, where shall we go next?
900046.feeling4: Being able to see everyone's smiles at the banquet makes all the hard work and preparation worth it.
900046.propose: So this means... "We'll always be forever?" Thank you very much. I'll gladly accept it - however... If anything was to happen to us, I hope that you would consider yourself first...
900046.drop_descrip: Kongou-class fast battleship number two – Hiei.
900046.skill: Be swept away by the raging waves!
900046.profile: I am Hiei, the first Kongou-class battleship born in the Land of the Rising Sun. As an Imperial Ship, I witnessed the growth of our mighty fleet, and led our forces into the Battle of the Solomon Sea. Commander, have you finished your preparations? The banquet is about to begin.
900046.touch2: Hehe. Commander, have you not gotten enough sleep yet?
900046.mission: Let's finish while we still have the momentum!
900046.home: Welcome back. The tea has just been brewed to the right temperature.
900046.expedition: Welcome back, everyone. Hopefully, none of you encountered any suspicious people?
couple_encourage: Are you still waiting for your sister?
900046.mail: Are all of these new letters? Thank you for your hard work.
900046.feeling3: That Kirishima... She's actually quite the popular one...

202125.detail: Whether serving my master or managing a restaurant, it is my responsibility as a Royal Maid to handle it promptly and efficiently. Now then, are you satisfied with my performance?
202125.touch: Yes, what can I get for you?
202125.login: Your menu. I would recommend our new offerings here. There is also a promotional campaign of which you might take advantage.
202125.main: Miss Fubuki is rather excitable, but she is a clever and hardworking girl. Just give her a bit of direction and she'll figure it all right out.|While the customer is free to order anything she wants, as a maid I feel it is my responsibility to offer healthier suggestions. Particularly to the Union girls who order litres and litres of cola...|Leading customers to their tables, organising shifts, management... all of this would make a fine training program for the Royal Maids.
202125.unlock: Welcome, table for one? Of course, right this way. Oh? What is it? Ah... I'm filling in for the manager at the moment, so that makes you my customer rather than my master, no?
202125.drop_descrip: Welcome, table for one? Of course, right this way. Oh? What is it? Ah... I'm filling in for the manager at the moment, so that makes you my customer rather than my master, no?
202125.touch2: While it is indeed a maid's duty to offer everything to her master... Not to be presumptuous, but you could consider the time and place.
202125.home: Here is the pizza you ordered. Do take your time and enjoy it.

401241.detail: Even off duty, I cannot remove this claw, as it is a symbol of my dignity! ...What do I do if I need to pick something up? Th-that's your job, you foolish mortal!
401241.touch: Do you want to stay by my side tht badly? Heheh~
401241.login: Are you all rested up? I'll give you the privilege of keeping me entertained today! Consider this your greatest honor, mortal!
401241.main: I shall reward you with a taste of this black fruit! Open your mouth, foolish mortal!|
401241.unlock: Come, human! The rite of festivities is upon us! Come hither, and let us revel in this foreign holiday together!
401241.drop_descrip: Come, human! The rite of festivities is upon us! Come hither, and let us revel in this foreign holiday together!
401241.touch2: Th-there are some things you just shouldn't do! I hope you're ready for some punishment, foolish mortal!

199022.detail: Seattle picked out this lace coverup for me. She's good with this kind of thing...
199022.touch: Commander, it's really funny watching you try to figure out where it's safe to look. Hahaha!
199022.login: Ooh, you're just in time. Commander, mind helping me set up this parasol?
199022.main: What do you think of my sunglasses? I dig them, personally. Hahaha!|Nothing beats an ice cold Oxy Cola on a summer day! Here, take one, Commander... Oh right, you can't drink these. This one's for you.|We've still got some summer left, so why not try to plan a "Beach World Tour" for us?
199022.unlock: Heh heh, the warm sun and the sea breeze really hit the spot, don't they? Alright, let's get out there and enjoy ourselves! That's what you've been waiting for, right, Commander?
199022.drop_descrip: Heh heh, the warm sun and the sea breeze really hit the spot, don't they? Alright, let's get out there and enjoy ourselves! That's what you've been waiting for, right, Commander?
199022.touch2: Ah haah? Commander, you've really gotten into the spirit of the beach now. Maybe I should give you a bit more "stimulation." Like a whooping with this parasol, for instance.
199022.home: Ooh, nice work on that sortie. Did you want an ice cream? I still have some here.

101380.detail: Just what are you looking at? You ought to hurry up and return to your post.
101380.login: Being punctual is a good habit to have, so please keep it up.
101380.feeling2: As long as we keep on winning, will we be able to bring an end to the war? Rather than searching for the answer to that question, it would be more practical to focus on winning the battles ahead of us.
101380.headtouch: What is... the meaning of this?
101380.mission_complete: Mission complete. However, your work doesn't end there.
101380.main: If you are tired, please take a break. If you were to collapse, the command chain would follow suit. |For me, no matter where I am, or what I am called, I will continue to fight on as long as I live. |I was born for battle and died for peace. Other than this fact, I won't dwell on anything else.
101380.feeling5: After discussing things with my sisters a bit, I realized that if the war actually ended, I wouldn't know how to do anything else... Eh, you'd stay with me and teach me yourself... so there would be no problem? E-ehhh?
101380.upgrade: Strengthening combat effectiveness is also an important link when it comes to battle.
101380.unlock: I am the Fletcher-class destroyer, Kimberly. From today onward, I will be one of your subordinates. Pleased to meet you.
101380.feeling4: Recently, I had a strange dream. I dreamt that I wasn't on the battlefield, but instead taking a walk along the port, hand-in-hand with someone close to me... Wh-what's so funny?
101380.feeling1: The incompetent will be weeded out by time. You are no exception.
101380.propose: S-so this is a promise ring... Really, I never could have imagined that this would happen to me... However, I'm truly, truly happy, from the bottom of my heart. Is this... the "love" that my sisters were talking about? Hey... don't laugh!
101380.skill: Let's put this needless battle to an end!
101380.profile: I am the Fletcher-class destroyer Kimberly. I am normally tasked with escort and anti-submarine duties, so should the need arise, please do not hesitate to deploy me.
101380.touch2: Do you want to pay a visit to the court martial?
101380.mission: As a commander, it is only fitting that you complete these tasks.
101380.home: I see you've returned at the scheduled time, Commander. However, you can't afford to take it easy just yet.
101380.win_mvp: This is a fine example of tactical synergy. Let's keep it up.
101380.feeling3: "What do I plan to do after the war is over?" Hmm... I've never given this much thought, nor have I wanted to. However, why did you bring it up all of a sudden?

900043.detail: The melody of my flute is a requiem for the dead. Shall I play it for you?
900043.touch: Commander, would you like to hear me play my flute?
900043.login: Intelligence is said to be a woman’s virtue, but that often puts me at odds with those senpai of mine. How troublesome~
900043.battle: The perfected aircraft carrier, {namecode:95}, setting sail!
900043.hp_warning: Pump water to the other side! Hurry!
900043.feeling2: My sister {namecode:96} and I held on for two years during the darkest of times. If only our senpai could have worked a little bit harder.
900043.mission_complete: We’re not going to carry out our plans of attrition warfare? Tch~
900043.main: To always be dealing with those senpai from the First Carrier Division... Commander, you must have a really strong liver.|Though our relationship was once one of victim and perpetrator, I look forward to working with you, Lexington.|{namecode:96}, if you keep causing trouble for our Eagle Union colleagues, you’ll only get tempura for dinner tonight~
900043.feeling5: Commander, could you lend me your shoulder? Sometimes, even I want to simply clear my mind and rest. When I get like that, can I depend on you to be by my side?
900043.unlock: As the flagship of the Fifth Carrier Division, I, Shoukaku, shall do my best to become as good as those esteemed senpai in the First Carrier Division, or something... *giggles* That was on purpose~
900043.feeling4: Those senpai are so sly! Just when I was about to overtake them, they went somewhere I could never reach! How unfair!
900043.feeling1: I think I just saw a future in which you were cut down by {namecode:91}, Commander.
900043.propose: The melody of my flute is like a flowing river, requiring an inspiration that usually can only be found atop a mountain. Just being by your side, however, inspires me even more.
900043.drop_descrip: First ship of the {namecode:95}-class aircraft carriers, {namecode:95}.
900043.skill: This is the privilege of being the elder sister!
900043.profile: I am {namecode:95}, the flagship of the Fifth Carrier Division. Because my super smart senpai went and got themselves all killed, I had to carry the flag of the Sakura Empire’s carrier divisions. Though I was more accomplished than them, for whatever reason, I was always considered weaker. Maybe it was due to my "lack of grace and speed" during my final moments... With that said, allow me to reintroduce myself. I am Shoukaku, the punching bag of the Sakura Empire. Please take care of me from now on~
900043.touch2: Commander, come and indulge yourself in {namecode:95}'s tenderness.
900043.mission: Let me take a look the mission... It’s not the Coral Sea? That’s too bad~
900043.home: The girls have returned safely to port, just like the Fifth Carrier Division always does.
900043.win_mvp: The Glory of the 5th Carrier Divison is here! *giggles*
900043.expedition: This is all required to carry out the Circle Five Plan.
couple_encourage: {namecode:96}, give it your all! I'll cover you!
Do you see my true power, {namecode:91}?
This time... I'll prove to you how powerful I really am!
I won't be able to protect you if you stray too far!
Where is the Queen of the Docks heading to?
900043.mail: We’ve got mail from HQ, they told us to carry out the Decisive Battle Doctrine. Heh, just kidding~!
900043.feeling3: Do I hold a grudge against the First and Second Carrier Divisions? Of course~ For them to leave us behind like that, wouldn’t anyone complain in that situation?
900043.lose: Hiryuu-senpai may be willing to fight until the bitter end, but... that’s not my style. What a shame~

900042.detail: You shouldn't ask about a maiden's weight so casually~ *giggles*
900042.touch: Oh my~ Are you going to give me a massage?
900042.login: Welcome back! What should we do today?
900042.battle: Naughty children need to be punished~
900042.hp_warning: Looks like big sis needs to get a little serious.
900042.feeling2: If you don't express your thoughts clearly, Commander, nobody will ever understand you.
900042.mission_complete: Mission complete! I wonder what rewards we will get~?
900042.main: It seems like... my shoulders are always sore...|Commander~ I can see you ogling me in a daze, you know?|Hup! A little bug got into the room. You didn't see it? I'm confident in my good eyesight.
900042.feeling5: It's no good... I can't control myself anymore! Commander, won't you become mine? You don't have to worry about anything... All you have to do is listen to me, and I'll satisfy all your needs...
900042.upgrade: My whole body feels... hot... Commander, can you stay with me for a bit?
900042.unlock: Oh my, what a cute commander! Please allow your big sister {namecode:67} to take good care of you from now on!
900042.feeling4: It's all your fault, Commander... If you make such a cute face, I won't be able to keep my hands off of you...
900042.feeling1: You've been naughty, Commander. Do you want to be punished so badly? *giggles*
900042.propose: Oh my, you've caught me, Commander. Or should I say, I've finally caught you? Hehe~ I'll never let you go now!
900042.drop_descrip: Second ship of the {namecode:66}-class heavy cruisers, {namecode:67}.
900042.skill: Oh my, how should I torment you today?
900042.profile: I'm {namecode:67}, the second ship of the {namecode:66}-class heavy cruisers and flagship of the Second Fleet. Many of my sisters have followed my banner into battle. No matter the mission, just leave everything to big sister here~!
900042.touch2: You can touch me even more if you'd like... but there's no saying what might happen next... *giggles*
900042.mission: Missions have been updated. Don't forget to take a look!
900042.home: Welcome back, Commander. Are you tired? Come bury yourself in big sister's bosom~!
900042.win_mvp: Combat operations... complete! It's all thanks to your leadership, Commander!
900042.expedition: The commission fleet is back! Let's go give them a warm welcome.
900042.mail: Ara~ new mail? I wonder who it's from.
900042.feeling3: Commander, would you like me to clean your ears? Come on, don't be shy. Just leave it to me~
900042.lose: Oh my... this is a bit troublesome...

103164.detail: Life is its own journey. You can't live the perfect life, but what's important is living without regrets.
103164.touch: Getting lost in a foreign land is no big deal as long as you've got friends.
103164.login: What's the plan for today, Commander? Feel like visiting a Sakura Empire shrine?
103164.main: What type of journey do you prefer? One that follows a strictly laid-out plan, or one where you go with the flow?|Why are these other puppies following me? ...You know what, it's all good. It's always good to have more company on a journey.|I'd love to take a shot at a Sakura Empire sport. Like archery. Or maybe kendo?
103164.unlock: "Our meeting here must have been preordained by fate. Hail to you. I am a passing traveler by the name of Baltimore." ...Hahah, it's nothing. Just some lines I came up with to match my traditional getup. Did they do the trick, Commander?
103164.drop_descrip: "Our meeting here must have been preordained by fate. Hail to you. I am a passing traveler by the name of Baltimore." ...Hahah, it's nothing. Just some lines I came up with to match my traditional getup. Did they do the trick, Commander?
103164.home: Brrr... Sure is windy today... Oh, hey, Commander. Not feeling cold, are you?

103102.detail: A photo op? Sure... Lemme make a pose~
103102.touch: Are you here to sit in, Commander?
103102.main: What did I learn in class? Dunno... the clouds outside looked really neat... |I saw a black cat on the way to school this morning... Wonder if it's some kind of omen? |Why isn't there some class just for spacing out...
103102.unlock: Off to school we go~ Being punctual makes me a good girl~
103102.drop_descrip: Off to school we go~ Being punctual makes me a good girl~
103102.touch2: Nyahh! Th-this is a violation of school rules!

106011.detail: That get up is the usual Long Island wearing her public face~ ... Want some potato chips?
106011.battle: Commander, can I just chill out back here?
106011.feeling2: You found out my secret, Commander... Oh well! Please don't tell anyone else, ok?
106011.main: Commander, don’t bother me, I’m really busy right now. Busy with what? Games! All of these stuipid friggin backlogged games!|Commander, I brought a bunch of snacks~ Should I give you some?|Commander, do you like High Grade or Magical Grade stuff? I even got Powerful Grade stuff too!
106011.feeling5: We need more co-op games, as well as tools... Eeeh, I don't wanna go outside~ Commander, for the sake of the future of the adorable Long Island~ Please buy this list up!
106011.unlock: Everyone's favorite and talked-about Long Island, actually has another hidden secret...
106011.feeling4: Commander, my room is not a game store~ Oh, you just want to play with me? F...Fine! I just bought a newly launched title. Wanna play it together?
106011.feeling1: Commander~ intruding into a person's room is against the law! I-I'm reporting you!
106011.drop_descrip: Everyone's favorite and talked-about Long Island, actually has another hidden secret...
106011.home: Good work out there, Commander. Time to relax~ Here you go, you're now Player 2
106011.feeling3: Are you free, Commander? Wanna play a game then? We can make plastic models too if you want.
106011.lose: Ah, Long Island has become... Tired Island...

105080.detail: Commander, I will do my best to meet everyone's expectations
105080.touch: This is comfy. Every time big sis scolds me, she comforts me with this afterwards as well.
105080.login: Weather, check. Wind, check. A fine sailing day, Commander.
105080.feeling2: You don't know if you can be friends with someone unless you tried to make them. Commander, wanna hang out together?
105080.main: I feel different from big sister? That's not true. She might not look it but she's actually kind|Ah~ Big sis didn't say much today... Wha! N-nothing at all!|Ah, where did my undies go? Eheh
105080.feeling5: Tennesee said to me, 'You must be careful who you choose as a partner.' 'Once you do, tell me', she also said. Well, if it's you, Commander, she won't say a word, I think...
105080.upgrade: Now I can reach for further waters~
105080.unlock: Hello, Commander. I am California. It's not good to brag, but I'm quite strong you know. Do look forward to it~
105080.feeling4: We've already had fun throughout the docks. How about we go some place farther? Just the two of us... Heh heh heh...
105080.feeling1: Commander, I'll go play on my own now~
105080.propose: Commander, where are we going to play today? ...WHA! ...Seriously, I don't... I'm happy and all, but please don't pull this again. You surprised me...
105080.drop_descrip: Tennessee-class battleship –  California, Hull Number BB-44!
105080.profile: Hello. I am the second of the Tennessee class battleships, California. I was once the flagship of the Pacific fleet, and was part of the Atlantic fleet as well. How about it? Bet you didn't expect that I was a popular one, did you? Hehe~
105080.touch2: Wait-... Commander! Where are you touching? Big sis wouldn't do this!
105080.mission: Commander, don't forget to do your missions!
105080.home: You looked great just now, Commander!
105080.win_mvp: Aaah... that was a great workout
105080.expedition: Commander, the girls from the commissions have returned. Let me do one next time, please~
105080.mail: It's new mail. Wanna open it up right away?
105080.feeling3: *humming* Ah, Commander~ Just who I was looking for. I was thinking about taking you some place to have fun!
105080.lose: Oof... Big sis will lecture me for sure!

202250.detail: Call you Producer? No thank you, Master works just fine for me. Or... would you prefer to be called a "pest?"
202250.touch: I may not have my gun with me, but you would still be wise to mind your conduct.
202250.login: I finished cleaning up the office before I have to head off for lessons. I'd appreciate it if you don't mess it up while I'm gone.
202250.battle: I will "clean up" the pests that seek to disrupt this concert.
202250.hp_warning: I still have a contingency plan.
202250.feeling2: I've had to suspend maid duties due to my idol unit activities. I will make up for lost time after this is done.
202250.mission_complete: So these are the royalties? I'm sure the other members will be pleased.
202250.main: I heard that there are some folks out there who get aroused from being abused by their favorite idol... I'll never understand. |Defeating enemies with song? Utterly unrealistic, but might make for an interesting school project. |To be honest, I'm a bit jealous of Belfast. Her talents are boundless, beyond just being a maid.
202250.feeling5: The girl who you like is not the maid or the shining star, but "Sheffield?" ...A stale confession, but thank you. I'll remember that.
202250.upgrade: I shall commit myself fully regardless of the workplace.
202250.unlock: I am Sheffield, from the Royal Maids. I will explain how this transpired to you, so please stop looking like the world has turned upside down.
202250.feeling4: I used to think that doing maid work would make other jobs seem trivial in comparison, but reality certainly had a very different message for me... If you dare tell anyone else about what I just said to you, I'll have to sew your lips together... Just kidding, don't take it that seriously.
202250.feeling1: To prevent harm from befalling the other members, I shall first eliminate you.
202250.propose: No matter what I am, I will always love you with all my heart and soul, my Master. ...I wasn't being facetious. Really.
202250.drop_descrip: I am Sheffield, from the Royal Maids. I will explain how this transpired to you, so please stop looking like the world has turned upside down.
202250.skill: May my song bring you eternal rest...
202250.profile: Town-class light cruiser, Sheffield. I am currently serving as an idol at Her Majesty's request. Do you have a problem with that?
202250.touch2: Surely you're aware of the consequences for doing such things to an idol?
202250.mission: A new offer? I shall prepare myself then.
202250.home: Ah, Master, welcome back~ You heard a weird voice, you say? It must've been your imagination.
202250.expedition: Do I need to pre-record a gunshot to remind you? ...A commission fleet has returned.
couple_encourage: Let's try to muster up a semblance of teamwork.
202250.mail: There's new mail. I'll make sure to respond to the fanmail.
202250.feeling3: I'm playing very well? Master, you are able to follow in my footsteps as well... as long as you dedicate yourself to practicing every day.
202250.lose: This failure was due to my incompetence. Sincerest apologies.

900044.detail: That Grey Ghost... I’d like to duel her just once.
900044.touch: My least favorite food? Turkey, of course.
900044.login: Where are we going today? Pearl Harbor? Or perhaps the Coral Sea?
900044.battle: A never-ending swarm of enemies? I’m already used to it.
900044.feeling2: Seniors and juniors... they’re all such a pain.
900044.mission_complete: Hmm... Seems like the situation has taken a turn for the better!
900044.main: {namecode:95} is so cute when she’s embarrassed!|Keep fighting until the last arrow is broken! That is what it means to be an elite!|Wait, Grey Ghost, don’t run away just because you won! Let’s have a rematch!
900044.feeling5: Commander, you make me feel just as if I am with Shoukaku. H-huh? That’s not it! I’m not treating you as my sister!
900044.upgrade: As a perfected aircraft carrier, I shall not lose to anyone, not even to my seniors or to the Grey Ghost herself.
900044.unlock: I am {namecode:96}, the last elite of the Sakura Empire’s Carrier Divisions. I can only be at my best when I am with my sister {namecode:95}.
900044.feeling4: Whenever I feel irritated or lost, training always makes me feel at ease. Yes, I’ll definitely get stronger and catch up to that Grey Ghost one day.
900044.feeling1: Commander, would you like a taste of the anguish I experienced during the Battle of the Marianas?
900044.propose: E-eh?! Th-this is... I’m not misunderstanding you, right? Then... um, from now on, I’ll be in your care, dar... darling? Waaah! Shoukaku is calling me!
900044.drop_descrip: Second ship of the {namecode:95}-class aircraft carriers, {namecode:96}.
900044.skill: As long as Shoukaku is with me~!
900044.profile: I’m {namecode:96} from the Fifth Carrier Divison, though I was assigned to the First Carrier Division at one point. Together with my sister Shoukaku, we became the last two elite carriers of the Sakura Empire. We triumphed in bitter battles against Lexington, Hornet, and even Enterprise. That’s right, I was even able to severely damage the Grey Ghost herself, although she proved to be luckier than me. My service came to an end when Lexington, risen from the dead, sunk me. In the end, I still completed my final mission and sank with no regrets.
900044.mission: Is it time for a break? Commander, you should come try some of {namecode:95}’s cooking!
900044.home: I’ll need you to perform some maintenance on me. Ah, don’t forget about the planes either!
900044.win_mvp: I am the auspicious crane, after all!
900044.expedition: If only I had more planes...!
couple_encourage: I'm fearless, as long as my sister is with me!
I don't know why, but I just find you terribly annoying...
That ties up the score. Next round decides the winner!
Uwah! When did you get here?!
I never thought I'd fight alongside the Grey Ghost herself!
900044.mail: So? Is it good news or bad news?
900044.feeling3: My fate always seems to be entertwined with Lexington’s... Ah~ Commander, please don’t tell Sara I said that. I can’t handle that girl.
900044.lose: Am I going to be sunk... again...?

199023.detail: The Sakura Empire's tea is good stuff! But I still feel like I want an Oxy-cola sometimes... Huh? It wouldn't look right? I can't help it if I want one.
199023.touch: Ready to be a proper escort?
199023.login: And just where are you escorting me today? I'm dying to find out.
199023.main: So this "Momotarou" pops out of a peach! What an amazing little guy!|Seattle, I got an invite to this party or something. Any idea for a talent show? It has to be something better than the "Georgia Beam"!|Commander, I just finished my new drink - mixi
199023.unlock: Happy New Year, Commander! I guess you dress up all flashy like this for the Sakura New Year. Would you escort me...? What are you gawking like that for...? Haha, am I so dazzling? Hahaha!
199023.drop_descrip: Happy New Year, Commander! I guess you dress up all flashy like this for the Sakura New Year. Would you escort me...? What are you gawking like that for...? Haha, am I so dazzling? Hahaha!
199023.touch2: Hey now, you're going to mess up my outfit.

102040.detail: What's the matter, Commander? You look kinda emotionless.
102040.touch: It's here, it's here! Want to head out now?
102040.login: Hey, Commander! I'll protect you, like I always do!
102040.battle: Look to the east! It's burning red!
102040.hp_warning: My hand is calling out to me to seize victory!
102040.feeling2: Only those who aren't afraid of death deserve to live! Ahh, don't be afraid Commander, I don't mean that literally! What I meant to say is that it's not about living or dying, it's about what mindset you have!
102040.mission_complete: Looks like our well-deserved rewards have been delivered.
102040.main: My motto is: "be the best at everything"!|Is the sun bigger in Argentina?|There's nothing more thrilling than coming back from the verge of death!
102040.feeling5: I see. It's no wonder that whenever I'm with you, I'm in such high spirits! I feel like my heart is on fire! This is it, this is love... I've never experienced this before...
102040.unlock: Are you the commander? I'm Phoenix. That's right, the legendary phoenix! Do you have what it takes to lead me?
102040.feeling4: Although I respect that man, you're still you, Commander. As long as you're with me, I'm invincible!
102040.propose: ... Thank you. I'll accept it. Also, um... I don't really know how to talk all sweet or flirt or anything like that, but now that you've chosen me, I promise I won't let you down!
102040.drop_descrip: Brooklyn-class light cruiser – Phoenix, Hull Number CL-46!
102040.profile: I'm Phoenix. I once escorted a certain important person. Just like a phoenix, no matter what happens to me, I'll always come back from death! Throw all the dangerous missions you've got at me, I won't let you down!
102040.mission: How could you fall behind on something as simple as missions?
102040.home: Looks like we made it back safe and sound as usual today!
102040.win_mvp: Hahah! Aren't there any strong enemies left for me to fight?
102040.expedition: Commission completed... Hey, isn't it about time you let me head out on one?
couple_encourage: C'mon sis, don't look so sad.
Chicken? I'm a phoenix!
102040.mail: Hey! Commander! Your mail is here!
102040.feeling3: What's the matter? If you're okay with me then I can give you some advice!
102040.lose: Tsk, I'll get you for this!

502051.detail: That Ying Swei... Even though she knows I'm not good with the literary stuff, she still made me think up spring couplets... If it wasn't for her sake... Commander, come here and help me think of lines as well!
502051.login: You're late, Commander! Jeez, we're all supposed to get together for the New Year, so stop running around!
502051.main: My performance for the Spring Festival banquet? ...I-i-it's not like I'm nervous or anything! I've practiced over and over!|I wish my sister was as demure and well-behaved as Tai Yuan... Yeah, Ying Swei, I'm talking about you! Stop laughing!|Commander, it's really cold tonight around the time of the banquet. If you catch a cold, um, I'm going to have to take care of you, and that would be a hassle... So, um, yeah!
502051.unlock: Happy New Year, Commander! This red envelope is my gift to you... after all, that's my responsibility as a big sister! Anyway, hurry up and take it!
502051.drop_descrip: Happy New Year, Commander! This red envelope is my gift to you... after all, that's my responsibility as a big sister! Anyway, hurry up and take it!
502051.touch2: Y-you're gonna get eaten up by the Nian beast!
502051.home: Don't worry, this tree is real sturdy and won't break with just one person on it... Hey, wait, are you calling me fat?!

900041.detail: Small strokes fell great oaks, constant drops pierce through rock. Those who train through the most humdrum of days shall seize victory in the most critical of moments. That is my belief.
900041.touch: E-enemies?! Oh... It was you, Commander? Apologies - my eyesight isn't the best.
900041.login: {namecode:66} standing by. What are your orders?
900041.battle: Please leave combat to me. I shall not shame my title of being "The Strongest!"
900041.feeling2: Do you need anything? If not, I'm going back to work.
900041.mission_complete: Mission accomplished! Are we going to collect the rewards?
900041.main: Even back in port, we must not lower our guard. Danger lurks around every corner.|Commander, not even you could withstand my blade.|Daily refinement means to continually strive towards your goals. Commander, may your focus never falter.
900041.feeling5: No matter how badly I'm injured, I will make sure to always return to your side. So... Commander, could you always stay with me as well?
900041.unlock: Are you the Commander? Please allow this lowly {namecode:66} to offer you what little strength she has.
900041.feeling4: Recently, I haven't been able to keep my composure during training.. Just from thinking about you, my form becomes sloppy. If I am like this, would you still want to keep me by your side?
900041.feeling1: A sword has no eyes. It would be wise to avoid approaching me casually.
900041.propose: For you to acknowledge me like this, Commander, is the greatest honor. From now on, this blade shall serve only you. Please continue to treat me kindly.
900041.drop_descrip: First ship of the {namecode:66}-class heavy cruisers, {namecode:66}.
900041.profile: I am {namecode:66}, first ship of the {namecode:66}-class heavy cruisers. I may not look like it, but I have already crossed through countless battlefields. Please place your faith in my firepower and armor, and be at ease.
900041.touch2: Kyaa! You scared me... how shameless!
900041.mission: New tasks have been assigned - would you like to confirm them?
900041.home: I'm glad that you came back safe and sound.
900041.win_mvp: Hm... Once again, I've cut a worthless object.
900041.expedition: Your fleet has returned from commission. Want to welcome them back?
900041.mail: Commander, there's new mail. Shall I bring it for you?
900041.feeling3: It might be pretty nice to just set aside my duties and have a relaxing conversation with you every once in a while, Commander.
900041.lose: I was careless... I definitely will not fail next time!

102110.detail: Commander, do you need anything? You can always chat with me if you're free.
102110.touch: Do you like getting physical too, Commander?
102110.login: Commander, did you do anything interesting while you were away for so long? You should bring me along next time~!
102110.feeling2: I've been to a lot of places, but this is the first time I've ever seen a fleet with girls from all around the world. This is so interesting!
102110.mission_complete: Teehee~ Our rewards have arrived, Commander! ... Or would you rather get a passionate hug from me instead?
102110.main: Commander, you've got something on your lips... Got it!|I'd love to be able to see everyone from all over the world~!|Lots of my sisters have survived through this war. Impressive, right?
102110.feeling5: Commander, I've seen a lot during my time in this world, but there's still one thing I haven't experienced yet since I don't have a partner...
102110.unlock: Hi! Are you the commander? That's great~! I'm Richmond. Hit me up whenever you feel like~!
102110.feeling4: This fleet is great! And you're awesome too, Commander! Let me tell you about myself... First thing: after that World War just before this one, I was...
102110.feeling1: Seems like I have to find another place...
102110.propose: That's right, I was talking about love! ... And the things that follow! I've never met a suitable candidate, at least until I met you~! When I accept this, it'll mean you agree to be my partner as well, right~?
102110.drop_descrip: Omaha-class light cruiser - Richmond, Hull Number CL-9!
102110.skill: Let me show you what a difference experience makes!
102110.profile: I'm Richmond of the Omaha-class. Because I'm an old model, I was mainly tasked with things like escorts and transport. Although my performance is nothing to brag about, you can say that I've seen a lot of action! Feel free to ask me anything whenever you have questions~!
102110.mission: ♪Mission here, mission there♪ Being a commander is so much work. Let me help you!
102110.home: You look so cool coming right off the battlefield, Commander!
102110.win_mvp: Teamwork makes the dream work! Yay!
102110.expedition: Commander, you can stare at me all day if you want, but just know that a commission has been completed.
102110.mail: Commander, I checked the mail box and brought your mail along with my own~
102110.feeling3: Commander~ I only just joined this fleet and there's still plenty I don't know yet. So, could I ask you to accompany me on a short walk?
102110.lose: Oh no, we lost... Well that sucks~

900040.detail: I've inspected the communication equipment. It won't cause any more problems...
900040.login: Commander, have you eaten yet? Here's some snacks.
900040.hp_warning: I don't want... to be alone...
900040.feeling2: Ayanami's impressions of Commander? I don't really know.
900040.headtouch: I don't really get it but... I'm a bit happy...
900040.mission_complete: The rewards for the previous mission are here.
900040.main: {namecode:6}'s ears... are they cute? I don't understand... As long as you're happy, Commander!|I've been having nightmares of all the girls getting lost... I'm certain that it's my fault, too...|Commander? No, nothing. I just wanted to see if you were here or not.
900040.feeling5: I don't particularly... like or dislike combat. I just do what must be done. But if it's for you, Commander... maybe I can get a bit stronger.
900040.unlock: I'm... Ayanami. I am often called the "Demon." Pleasure to meet you.
900040.feeling4: If there's one thing that worries me... it would be when you are not at my side.
900040.feeling1: I don't really want to get any closer.
900040.propose: Rest assured... This time, no matter what happens, I'll survive and return to you... because I'll always want to see you again...
900040.drop_descrip: First ship of special Type II {namecode:6} class destroyers, {namecode:6}.
900040.skill: Bear witness to the true power of the "Demon"
900040.profile: I am Ayanami, an improved Fubuki-class destroyer. I am not afraid of combat. Though just a destroyer, I can fight any enemy...
900040.touch2: Commander... please... don't touch there so much... It's making me feel weird...
900040.mission: Commander, we've been notified of new missions.
900040.home: Commander, you're a little like me on the battlefield... That's... pretty cool.
900040.win_mvp: MVP? I don't really get it, but... thanks.
900040.feeling3: Commander, you're always saying that my ears are cute... But why won't you touch them?

502050.detail: Why do people think Ying Swei is the big sister?! ...Am I that immature in comparison?! Commander, what's your take on this?
502050.login: H-hey, you're late! I was worried about you, darn it!
502050.battle: P-purge all evil... Ah, screw it, will you die already?!
502050.hp_warning: It's time to get serious! I'll make them pay for underestimating me!
502050.feeling2: I still haven't practiced my dance today... Commander?! I, I won't let you peek!
502050.headtouch: Ahhhh!! You're gonna mess it up, so stop touching already!
502050.mission_complete: That mission was a piece of cake! ...W-well, I suppose your efforts helped!
502050.main: Let Ying Swei handle the public side of things! I, uh, I'll support her from the sidelines! ...Wait, wouldn't that make me seem like the little sister then?!|H-how long are you going to keep dawdling around in front of me? Can you just sit down and get your work done?! Eh? ...What the heck are you saying?! It's not like I really care what you're doing or anything...!|Only through perseverance can we reach our desired outcome! ...Th-those are Ying Swei's words, not mine!
502050.feeling5: About my new dance, um... I want you to name it, since you'll be the first person who gets to see it. So... how about it? Y-you don't have to come if you don't want to! ...Ugh! I mean, you have to come! No matter what! Even if you don't want to! Jeez!
502050.upgrade: H-hey, I look a bit more reliable now, don't I?
502050.unlock: I'm Chao Ho, lead ship of the Chao Ho-class cruisers! Don't you forget it! Oh, and no matter what Ying Swei says, don't let her trick you into thinking I'm the little sister!
502050.feeling4: Um, Ying Swei said you don't like short-tempered girls, so I'll try to act a bit mellower! So, um, please don't hate me... Hey, wh-what are you laughing for?! Don't get all uppity with me!
502050.feeling1: Don't talk to me like you know me!
502050.propose: At a time like this, I'm supposed to say "may we hold hands and hope to live forever with one another" or something like that, right... Ahh, I can't remember this stuff! A-anyway, you have to take good care of me from now on! Got it?!
502050.drop_descrip: Chao Ho-class protected cruiser – Chao Ho.
502050.skill: Be captivated by my song and dance!
502050.profile: I'm the name ship of the Chao Ho-class protected cruisers, Chao Ho! As for my history... who the heck knows! Specs? Dunno about that either! Stop asking about this stuff already!
502050.mission: We've got new missions! Hurry up and take a look! Otherwise, Ying Swei is going to complain about me nagging again!
502050.home: All right, nobody's here, right? Maybe I'll practice my dance steps a little... Ehh?! Huh... Wh-when'd you get back?!
502050.win_mvp: Hmph! I'll say this again! Don't you dare violate our oceans!
502050.expedition: The commission fleet's back? Y-yeah, we did send one out earlier, huh... Wh-what, I didn't forget about that!
couple_encourage: Let's do this thing!
I'm glad we have such stalwart companions!
502050.mail: Commander, hurry up and check your mail before it starts growing moss!
502050.feeling3: Commander! Ying Swei... Ying Swei... she threatened to not share Ning Hai's steamed buns with me! And said I have to clean the room today! H-hurry up and do something about her!
502050.lose: Guh... Am I still not strong enough yet...?

301471.detail: Was I able to bring you even the slightest bit of therapeutic benefit, Commander?
301471.touch: I, I'm not sure I can handle this kind of touching...
301471.login: Commander, today's your day off, so you don't have to work so hard, alright?

301471.drop_descrip: What's the matter, Commander? Oh, this outfit? ...Um, I heard that this outfit would bring you therapeutic benefits and hoped to try it on... Wh-what do you think? Does it feel therapeutic to you?
301471.home: Commander, would you like a shoulder massage? Ah, um, this level of contact is fine! I appreciate the courtesy!

899011.detail: I have no serious objections to sitting up here, but... there is one thing I cannot figure out. Are you perhaps deriving pleasure from seeing me up here like this?
899011.touch: My weapon is always within reach. Should you will it, I am ready to sortie at any time.
899011.login: Commander, making me sit up here waiting for you by myself is a tribulation in its own right.
899011.main: So I've managed to capture your gaze? Your eyes are... Nevermind, it doesn't bother me.|My arbitration is needed? ...Very well, please excuse me for a moment. I will make sure to hear them out.|As the one guiding this fleet forward... Commander, you are the one best suited to this throne.
899011.feeling5: As a servant of God, there is no need for vanity— Having that said, as the recipient of your love, you are free to make any arrangements that please you. After all, great and permissive is God's love.
899011.unlock: With all due respect, Commander, this finery and this throne are not fit for one such as myself. Despite the hallowed name I have inherited, I am nothing more than a warrior. —However, if such an arrangement pleases you, then I shall hold my objections.
899011.drop_descrip: With all due respect, Commander, this finery and this throne are not fit for one such as myself. Despite the hallowed name I have inherited, I am nothing more than a warrior. —However, if such an arrangement pleases you, then I shall hold my objections.
899011.home: I would much rather wield my spear upon the seas of battle than sit up here like a statue, Commander.

101249.detail: Hey, Commander~ You look like you're free, so let's play a game.
101249.touch: Ahahahahaha! That tickles! Stop it, Commander! Okay, I'm sorry! I'm sorry for pranking you! Ahahahahaha!
101249.login: Commander, would you rather have an ultra-spicy or ultra-salty cake~?
101249.main: That thing when you think you've been pranked even though I haven't actually done anything is a prank of sorts, too~|Hmm... You've gotten too used to my old bag of tricks, so it's time to come up with some new ones! ... Whoops, sorry~ First, I'll need to finish all this work~|Hey, Commander~ Don't you agree Hammann's reaction when she got pranked was just hilarious?
101249.unlock: Y'know, Commander~ No matter how nice you are to me, I'm still going to prank you~ Oh, but if you want my help with pranking others, I'll consider it~ Heehee~
101249.drop_descrip: Y'know, Commander~ No matter how nice you are to me, I'm still going to prank you~ Oh, but if you want my help with pranking others, I'll consider it~ Heehee~
101249.home: Well done, Commander~ Hmm? I'm not pulling any pranks today! Even I know there's a time and place for everything~ Heeheehee~

899010.detail: Commander, have you come here to offer your prayers to God?
899010.touch: I fight so that there may be peace. That is the single role that I can play.
899010.login: Bonjour, Commander. Please instruct me, what should we do next?
899010.battle: You shall all be purged equally!
899010.feeling2: So this is the land that I was promised... Tell me, will this place be Sodom, or Canaan?
899010.mission_complete: While rewards may certainly be nice... I have no interest in them.
899010.main: Commander, your time should not be squandered here. Leave the chores to me. |If there are any disputes within our ranks, allow me to handle the arbitration. That is my specialty. |Just winning the battle alone is enough to satisfy me, but you, Commander, ought to look far beyond that.
899010.feeling5: I finally understand now, Commander. What I experience now is the same as my sisters in arms - nay, perhaps even more fulfilling. Being a part of this fleet, by your side... is truly my Canaan.
899010.upgrade: For the sake of the role that we all must play...
899010.unlock: It is an honor to meet you at last - my prophet, my leader. I am Saint Louis, brought to your side by God's will. As long as it is justice that guides your hand, then this humble spear shall be yours to wield.
899010.feeling4: I feel like I have earned the acceptance of the fleet. However, is this truly the land that I was promised? ... No, I do not mean to cast doubt upon anyone. I merely feel that... I may yet have a deeper purpose.
899010.feeling1: My sisters in arms here may be righteous, but not you. Prepare to face divine punishment, sinner.
899010.propose: This I do swear. Your joy is my will, your victory is my glory, and the place that I can call home, is by your side... Blessed be the Lord who has brought me together with you - my commander, my love, and... my light.
899010.profile: Because ruination befell my homeland, I was returned to nothingness before I was born. As I am now, I am but an illusion, a manifestation of an ideal. But as long as you continue to lead my way, I shall in return clear all obstacles standing before yours.
899010.mission: Commander, it may not be the will of God, but you do have new missions issued from headquarters.
899010.home: Suffering is the brand of a warrior. Everyone, I'm proud of you for making it through.
899010.win_mvp: Ashes to ashes, dust to dust...
899010.expedition: Commander, my sisters in arms have returned from their commission.
899010.mail: Commander, does it not matter if these letters remain unopened?
899010.feeling3: I see my sisters in arms smile every day as if without a worry in the world. Perhaps this is their Canaan...
899010.lose: My Lord, why have you abandoned me...

101451.detail: Thanks for popping in! By the way... I'll pay you back for the OJ later.
101451.touch: You know what, it's comfier to sit and take it easy, so I'm gonna stay put for now.
101451.login: Welcome, Commander! Uh, watch your step!

101451.unlock: Welcome, Commander! I would fetch you our menu, but I've had a teensy accident here... Don't worry, I'll fix this somehow!
101451.drop_descrip: Welcome, Commander! I would fetch you our menu, but I've had a teensy accident here... Don't worry, I'll fix this somehow!
101451.touch2: Hey! You can't grope a staff member!

202019.touch: Commander?! Have I made some sort of mistake?!

202019.drop_descrip: Greetings, Commander. I hope I can ask for your continued guidance. ... Hm? Oh dear... I'm Leander, don't you recognise me?

101319.detail: You can let me handle all the work you don't have to go outdoors for...
101319.main: These torpedoes... could work as a half-decent pillow replacement.|It's not like I sleep all day EVERY day... But that's not to say I like moving around when awake...|Nicholas has a dream... A dream of becoming a statue...
101319.unlock: Commander, what month is it...? I think I overslept a bit... am I taller than I was before? *Yawn*... Gotta be because I slept the whole time...
101319.drop_descrip: Commander, what month is it...? I think I overslept a bit... am I taller than I was before? *Yawn*... Gotta be because I slept the whole time...

105019.detail: Commander, want to go horseback riding together? It doesn't matter if you don't know how, just hang on to my waist!
105019.touch: So, you fancy a dance with the devil? As you can see, I'm ready to up the ante. Young'un, what are you going to wager?
105019.login: Nevada, always ready for your orders!
105019.battle: As long I am here, there's no way we can lose!
105019.main: That Oklahoma, she's ain't so wet behind the ears anymore. Soon she's gonna be all independent. |Though fighting can't eliminate every problem in the world, it certainly can eliminate most of those who would cause problems. |Commander, I've got your back, so you can keep charging forward!

105019.drop_descrip: Heh, with this, I won't be outperformed by those fancy greenhorn battleships. Young'un, from now on, just leave everything to Nevada here!

202128.detail: I'm not going to give up being your maid. Besides, who could understand you better than me?

202128.login: Is today the same as usual?

202128.feeling5: Am I getting used to my new role? You really asked me a tough question, but...there's no sweeter question in the world.
202128.unlock: Are you destined for me? Greetings. Belfast, from this moment onwards, I will always be with you.
202128.drop_descrip: Are you destined for me? Greetings Belfast, from this moment onwards, I will always be with you.
202128.touch2: W-wait a moment...honestly, I'm cleaning right now..

107990.detail: Vestal gets way too worked up when I get even the tiniest of scratches... It's really not that big of a deal...
107990.touch: D-did you have advice for me? Ah, please share it with me!
107990.login: Commander, what will you teach me today?
107990.hp_warning: This... is nothing I can't handle!

107990.upgrade: One step closer to becoming the strongest!

107990.feeling1: Perhaps... You're the one who requires more learning, Commander...?
107990.propose: Does this mean... you're proud of my achievements? ...But, I still have so much to learn... Until I become a true hero, you have to stay by my side!
107990.drop_descrip: Yorktown-class aircraft carrier – Enterprise, Hull Number CV-6.
107990.profile: No matter how strong the enemy is, no matter how bad things get, fight with everything you have, and seize victory - that's the motto I strive for! As long as I keep working to get stronger, I know I'll be able to do it!
107990.touch2: Huh...? I'm not sure I understand this order, Commander...
107990.mission: A new mission? Yes, let's get ready... Huh? It's just for you?
107990.home: Commander, how was my performance just now? Is there anything, anything I could do better?
107990.win_mvp: Yay, I got number one again!
107990.expedition: Commission complete! If we get enough supplies, the fight on the front lines will get that much easier!
couple_encourage: Come at me all you want; I'll always win!
Such unexpected power... but I won't lose to you!
You won't surpass me so easily!
Take a good look at how far I've come!
Seriously, I told you, it's just a tiny scratch!
What is it like to become a true hero? ...I need to know!
107990.feeling3: Why do I want to become the strongest shipgirl? So that I can protect my friends, defeat our enemies, and put an end to this war. That's why!

304011.touch: You're awestruck by my beauty? Hehe, something as obvious as that needs not even be said~

304011.drop_descrip: We must fully live in the present, whether during work or during leisure - this is my mantra. Commander, shall we go for an outing together?
304011.touch2: You... perhaps you're going to need a remedial course in basic etiquette.

207110.detail: One, two, one two, Ah... Thank you, Commander. I'm not sure why I just can't keep my balance...
207110.touch: Are we practicing for handshake events? All right, thank you very much, Commander.

207110.upgrade: It's not just about the shining image, it's also about conveying one's voice.

207110.feeling1: I do hope my song can return you to normal, Commander...
207110.propose: I can feel your support, and your hope for me... And I see your eyes full of happiness as you look upon the stage, and upon me, Commander. Hehehe.
207110.drop_descrip: I am the newest addition to the Muse System, Illustrious. Through my songs, I shall spread the light of love and peace— Don't you think that's a wonderful thing?
207110.skill: I will bring the light to you in song.
207110.profile: I am the name ship of the Illustrious-class armored carriers... Oh, should I call myself "Idol Illustrious" now? I lack experience, but I will do what I must for the sake of peace.
207110.touch2: Commander, do remember to maintain decorum when touching an idol.

207110.home: ♪~Ooh, welcome back, Commander. Can you give our new song a listen?
207110.win_mvp: Our stage is brilliant and dazzling. Hehe~
207110.expedition: It seems the commission team has returned. I wonder if they have the material for Victorious's clothes...?
couple_encourage: You like hugs...?
207110.mail: Reading fan letters is so delightful. What about your mail, Commander?
207110.feeling3: At the Commander's request, I referenced a song by Comet and the girls. The gentle melody and soothing voices made me truly understand how idols can make people smile.
207110.lose: It seems the power of song alone was not enough...

404011.drop_descrip: A festival, huh? Going for days without fighting is boring, not to mention not my style. C'mon, Commander, isn't there *something* exciting I can do during this "Lunar New Year" festival?

304010.detail: The only value of war is the peace that follows it. I implore you to never forget this.
304010.login: Have you had enough rest? The fleet now awaits your orders.
304010.hp_warning: Now is the time to make our comeback!
304010.feeling2: Commander, please be at ease, for victory shall soon come.
304010.mission_complete: Excellent! We're one step closer towards our ultimate victory.
304010.main: No way in hell a battleship like me is going to get taken out by some flimsy torpedo! |Come! Let's destroy our enemies, pass through that measly canal, and return to the land where I was born! |I take myself too seriously? No, you take yourself too lightly! |Horns? Oh, these things? They're just decorations on the hat. I wouldn't look much like a member of the Sakura Empire without them, right?
304010.feeling5: That Hiei, trying to throw a party again tonight... Commander, do you have time to keep me company there?
304010.upgrade: Phew... another trump card to add to my hand.
304010.unlock: I am Kongou, lead ship of the Kongou-class battlecruisers. I shall illuminate the path that leads to victory!
304010.feeling4: I've heard that people are most likely to reveal their sentiments at twilight... I wonder if you're also like this?
304010.propose: Since you've put so much effort into pursuing me so passionately, it is only fitting that I give you the proper respect. Come, you've earned my hand.
304010.drop_descrip: Kongou-class fast battleship number one – Kongou.
304010.profile: Nameship of the Fast Battleships, flagship of the 7th Combined Fleet, and the last Sakura capital ship to be laid down overseas - that is me, Kongou!
304010.touch2: Hey you, don't tell me you've been subjecting my sisters to such depravity as well!?
304010.mission: Do I need to go do it myself?
304010.home: Good work out there. Were you able to achieve your tactical goals?
304010.win_mvp: To be victorious is to be elegant!
304010.expedition: Phew... time to take a break. Commander, does black tea suit you?
couple_encourage: Fast battleship squadron, sortieing！
Let's pursue victory together!
W-watch out for enemy fire!
Being popular... is best saved for when you're off the battlefield.
304010.mail: Adjust your strategies in accordance with the new information.
304010.feeling3: Will Zuikaku be fine on her own...? Mm... I'll watch her from here. From this distance, she probably won't notice me...
304010.lose: Please rest at ease. This situation can still be salvaged.

301219.touch: A-after my retrofit, I should now be someone you and my friends can depend on...
301219.login: I've grown now and should be able to handle secretary work! I-I'll be just fine... I think...

301219.drop_descrip: Hatsuharu, retrofit complete... H-hopefully I'm a little bit stronger now...

10500010.touch: Commander, do you need my help with something?

10500010.headtouch: Uwaah~ Ahaha, p-please have mercy~ My ears are really ticklish~

10500010.feeling5: I've grown to really like this place. Of course, I feel the same way about you, Commander!
10500010.upgrade: Right, right! That's the feeling of getting stronger~!
10500010.unlock: We meet at last! I'm Hololive's virtual fox, Shirakami Fubuki! Commander, now that you've called me, we're gonna have a foxin' good time! Now then, let's get to work!
10500010.feeling4: Commander, thanks for supporting me all this time! All right, we're going to throw a barbecue party tonight! Maybe I should... invite Kawakaze as well~
10500010.feeling1: Commander, you really suck at this, huh... Oh well~ I'll help you out. Let's clear this stage together!
10500010.propose: Thank you so much, Commander! I'll keep striving to improve for your sake, so please continue to look after me as well! Of course, you've also worked hard as well. Good job, good job!
10500010.drop_descrip: We meet at last! I'm Hololive's virtual fox, Shirakami Fubuki! Commander, now that you've called me, we're gonna have a foxin' good time! Now then, let's get to work!

couple_encourage: Twice the Fubuki, twice the fun!

Hololive Fleet, set sail!
10500010.mail: Ah, wait, the mail's here... Ohh, this one's addressed to you, Commander~ Maybe I'll let the others read it~
10500010.feeling3: Woah, we really stayed up late chatting, didn't we... But doing this every once in a while is pretty fun. Right, Commander~♫
10500010.lose: Nya! Isn't this difficulty setting a bit strange, nya?!

101382.detail: There are many differences between the Eagle Union and the Dragon Empery, but the one thing that doesn't change no matter where you are is everyone's desire for a better future.
101382.touch: There's still a lot of work left to do... but don't worry, Commander! Let's knock it out together!
101382.login: There is a proverb from the Dragon Empery: "A day's plans begin in the morning." Even if it's not the morning though, don't you think it's important to start off on the right foot, Commander?
101382.headtouch: C-Commander, the buns are going to get messed up...
101382.mission_complete: Mission complete. Commander, want to take a break?
101382.main: My friends from the Dragon Empery told me about a lot of fascinating legends! Commander, do you want to hear them too? |Recently, I tried to learn the bamboo flute. Commander, want to give it a listen? |Ugh... calligraphy is really difficult...
101382.feeling5: When I'm with you, I feel energized and my productivity goes through the roof. Perhaps... this is your magic spell? Hehe~
101382.unlock: When I change into clothes from the Dragon Empery, I can't help but to reminisce about the time I spent there... Commander, which style of clothes do you prefer - Union, or Empery?
101382.drop_descrip: While wearing clothes from the Dragon Empery, I can't help but reminisce about those days... Hehe, Commander, do you prefer me in Empery-style clothes, or Union-style clothes?
101382.touch2: Commander... you could go to jail for this, you know?
101382.mission: If you put things off for tomorrow, you'll find that there's always another tomorrow. That's why you shouldn't put off today's missions for tomorrow.
101382.home: Every time I return to port, I feel a wave of relief wash over me. Is this what "home" is?

10500020.detail: Next time, how about I invite Her Majesty Elizabeth and we livestream a horror game together? It sounds exciting, I'm pumped~
10500020.touch: Did something unpleasant happen? If you're alright with me, I'm willing to lend you an ear, or two, so relax~.
10500020.login: Welcome back, Commander! Let's do our best today, as always!
10500020.battle: Those aren't ally ships! ... That must mean they're enemies, right?
10500020.hp_warning: I absolutely can't stop, won't stop!
10500020.feeling2: I heard that this world has "Horror games" too! Sigh, I wish Friendo A were here so we could play... ah, Friendo A is my best friend. She's tiny, but she's a super reliable girl!
10500020.mission_complete: We're done with the mission! Yaaay~!
10500020.main: The little'uns at the port... I think they're called "Meowfficers"? They're soooo cute!|I heard there are live stages in this world too! It'd be sooo nice if I could put on a show with everyone else sometime...|I've tried changing into all sorts of clothes, but this look sho is the best after all! It helps me relax, but... I sure wish I had sleeves!
10500020.feeling5: Having come to this world with everyone, and meeting with Commander... there has been a lot of trouble here and there, but now, here I am cheering everyone on with you! It makes me really happy!
10500020.upgrade: Careful that you don't scratch anything! Let's goooo!
10500020.unlock: Hey Commander, it's nice to meet you~! I'm Tokino Sora, a virtual idol affiliated with Hololive! I'll do my absolute best here like I always do! I'll be in your care, so cheer me on, Commander!
10500020.feeling4: I... have no confidence that I'm properly being a reliable mentor... but when I look at you trying so hard, I can't help but think to myself that I can't let myself be so beaten down!
10500020.propose: Commander, I can do my best in this world because I'm with you. That's why all I can think is that I'd be happy if I could be make you feel even a bit better with my unending support...! Hehe... once again, I'll be in your care!
10500020.drop_descrip: Hey Commander, it's nice to meet you~! I'm Tokino Sora, a virtual idol affiliated with Hololive! I'll do my absolute best here like I always do! I'll be in your care, so cheer me on, Commander!
10500020.skill: For bad kids who don't listen... take this!
10500020.profile: I'm Tokino Sora, a virtual idol affiliated with Hololive! Ah, I guess I'd be Aircraft Carrier Tokino Sora here. I'm still inexperienced as an aircraft carrier, but please support me with all your energy!

10500020.mail: I wonder where in the world this letter came from?

10500020.lose: At times like this, let's let out a roar and calm down!

10500030.touch: Hm? Did you have something you wanted to request of the strongest maid, me?

10500030.upgrade: Did I become stronger? Hm, I see, I get it, I get it.
