10500030.feeling4: THIS IS IT. The results of my special Royal Navy maid training! Genuine Royal Navy black tea! Yep, as expected of me! That I'd be able to perfectly grasp the hang of this in such a short period of time! ... Hm? The taste is weird? There'z nowai!
10500030.feeling1: I, Minato Aqua, will soon be graduating from this post. While it has been a short while, thank you for all you've done for me all this time.
10500030.propose: This is... a Promise Ring?! Commander, this would... waitholdonasecond, with this you mean to say that you're no longer the Commander but "Master"... not that even, nono Master is "Master" but in a different sense and... Um, "Darling," was it? Oh no... it's embarrassing... Commander, is it really okay for me to have this? Ehehe, thanks, Darling…
10500030.drop_descrip: G-Good Aquafternoon...! I'm Minato Aqua, the Gamer Maid from Hololive~ U-Ugh... I didn't know I would have to introduce myself in this outfit!
10500030.profile: The Virtual Maid of Hololive! I'm often called clumsy and careless, but... that's not true!
10500030.mission: Commander, I'll stay with you as long as it takes you to finish your missions.
10500030.home: "Welcome back, Master!" or something. Wasn't that super maid-like?! Well then, I'll leave the cleaning of the office and preparation of dinner to you~
10500030.expedition: Commander! The Commission Team has brought a ton of materials back!
couple_encourage: Gammadion Gang, let's go! Is this the true power of the Royal Maids... I guess I'll have to do my best, too!
10500030.mail: Mail directed at the Commander, let's take a peek... Eww! What's with all the naval jargon?!
10500030.feeling3: Useless maid?! Failen Angel?! You're so cruel, Commander! If it's just something like warming up the bath, I can do it with no issues!
10500030.lose: I'm donezo!! I'm sorry, I'm sorry, I'm sorry, I'm telling you, I'm really sorry!!!

107060.detail: Want to look at my medal collection?
107060.login: You've come. If it's fighting, I'm ready for it any time.
107060.feeling2: It is my wish to live honestly and sincerely. That's why I'll speak my mind if I have something to say. You too should do the same without holding back.
107060.main: Is it you, Commander? ...Recently, I'm thinking about whether or not I can engage in anti-submarine actions...|Luck is also a part of strength? Then if possible, I'd like to impart some of it to my older sister.|So long as we live, there are things that will never go our way. When we die, it must happen in a way that carries no regrets.
107060.feeling5: What do you want to do after the war? --Me? I'll probably stick with you. I feel the safest out of battle when I'm with you. Will you... take me along with you?
107060.upgrade: I will show you... what lies at the end of power
107060.unlock: Second ship of the Yorktown class, Enterprise, reporting for duty. I will neither sympathize nor hold back with my enemies, and instead, I go all out. Such is my way.
107060.feeling4: There's no meaning in being peerless. As long as you are here, Commander, I can draw upon all of my strength. Let us end this war.
107060.feeling1: ...Commander, you don't seem to have enough courage
107060.propose: I carry with me the hopes and wills of the countless battlefields and goodbyes that I have experienced. Commander, are you prepared to shoulder them all? …I see. Then let us walk together until the end of our lives.
107060.drop_descrip: Yorktown-class aircraft carrier ー Enterprise, Hull Number CV-6!
107060.profile: I am the Yorktown class aircraft carrier, Enterprise. "Grey Ghost" is one of the many nicknames I have. My smoke-covered and bloodstained battle record is a reminder of my mission. I will continue to be victorious until the war ends.
107060.mission: Commander, your missions are not yet completed.  Hurry up and set off!
107060.home: It's one battle after another, huh...
107060.win_mvp: Commander, tell me. How many more do I have to sink?
107060.expedition: I've been on the battlefield for a long time, so I know about the importance of logistics. Commander, let's greet the girls who work hard behind the scenes.
couple_encourage: Teaming up with old rivals doesn't feel so bad.
Time to show you the true meaning of invincibility!
Such a playful old partner!
Brave Eagles, we fight until the end!
Heh, want to square off against me?
We all know each other. Come on, let's go!
All right, let me see what you're made of!
I'm counting on you. Don't fall behind!
I feel like... if you were there, then Akagi could have...
So this is... the power of friendship...
Don't worry, I'm right here.
107060.feeling3: All the lights in the sky are stars, just as all the lights on the seas are enemies... Commander, will there be a day where there's no more fighting?
107060.lose: I've lost after giving my all. I'm not regretting this...

403080.detail: Everyone is enjoying these idol activities, but aren't you forgetting about our weapons? I shouldn't worry about them...?
403080.touch: You want a hug? Sure, any time~
403080.login: Commander, what am I doing today? Orders please.
403080.battle: You stand in our way...? Then you will suffer!
403080.hp_warning: You're in the way... and you will pay!
403080.feeling2: Everyone is working so hard at this idol business, for your sake~ Me? Of course I am~ My smile and my joy, it's all for you, Commander... Hehehe♪
403080.mission_complete: You've been working just as hard as me. Good job, Commander~
403080.main: First I heal everyone with my soothing song, then I shred them with its power. Hehehe, I know how it works.|That Sakura girl, she's fragile; she can't take many hits... What can I do to help her?|I must pour my heart into my song... I may not be very good, but I'll try my best.
403080.feeling5: I thought slaughtering my enemies was the only way to make me feel better, but you taught me another way, Commander. I never thought you'd be able to change me. You really must... pay for that♡
403080.upgrade: There is something intruiging about using sound as a weapon~
403080.unlock: Heavy cruiser Roon, reporting for idol activities and associated experimental equipment testing. Today, we fight not with fire and sword, but with the power of song.
403080.feeling4: Knowing that the Commander is watching me sing brings some fulfillment to my empty heart. Maybe... as you give me your time, you also give me your life... is that the feeling?
403080.feeling1: Would you like to be my "enemy," Commander...? Hehehe... hehehehehehe...!!!
403080.propose: "Something too perfect and beautiful to destroy."――I never knew my concert could be so great. I want to perform more, to shine more, to take more and more of your time, Commander... until it runs out♪ Hehehe...
403080.drop_descrip: Heavy cruiser Roon, reporting for idol activities and associated experimental equipment testing. Today, we fight not with fire and sword, but with the power of song.
403080.profile: I am Iron Blood Cruiser Roon. I'm currently equipped with special "Muse System" rather than my usual loadout. It's definitely "special," but it is combat ready, and I can't wait to tear something apart with it. Thank you for this, Commander.
403080.touch2: Let's enjoy some "intimacy" a little later~
403080.mission: A combat mission? Yes! I'd love to join~
403080.home: Well fought. I got you a little something to eat, just as a way of saying thanks for all the training~
403080.win_mvp: Oooh this feeling... when I tear them to pieces...!
403080.expedition: The commission girls are back. Would you like to try, Commander? Line up for hugs, everyone~
403080.mail: You've got mail~ I wonder what's inside?
403080.feeling3: I feel a certain emptiness after working at this idol thing for a while... Maybe it's the combat... could it be because I can't sink as many as I used to...?
403080.lose: Hm... I still think we should be fighting with conventional weapons.

201261.drop_descrip: Ah, Commander, over here! Hm, you're going to take care of all the plans for today's date? In that case, I look forward to seeing just how suave you can be! Hehe~

201030.touch: Umm... if we walk so close together, people might misunderstand...
201030.login: Want some snacks, Commander? I saved some for you.

201030.feeling2: Say, Commander, do you think we get along with each other very well? Yes, yes! I too, think that you are very much like a close friend!

201030.feeling1: I was mistaken for being so friendly with you... I'm sorry...

201030.touch2: Whaa! This kind of thing... At least wait until you're at home!

201030.lose: Wha! Hurry and retreat, or else we'll get heatstroke!

301480.detail: Hehe~ You wanna play with me, Commander?

301480.propose: Woohooooo! I feel I could explode with how happy I am! Not literally, obviously~ Commander, I love you so much!

301480.touch2: Argh! I'll turn you into red paste!

couple_encourage: I'm rooting for you~!

301480.feeling3: Commander, Commander! I wanna play with you! We could call over Umikaze and Kawakaze, too!

10600020.login: Good work, Commander! Wait, you're starting work now?
10600020.hp_warning: Oh no, oh no... I'm in big trouble here!
10600020.feeling2: Mmh! The weather's so nice, I feel great~ Let's take a stroll around the port!
10600020.headtouch: Hehehe, this makes me feel happy...
10600020.mission_complete: Mission complete! Wow, and they give you this many rewards for it?! Commander, you're amazing!
10600020.main: I learned a lot of things from Marie today!|Yaaawn... Everything's so fuzzy... I-I'm not asleep!|Commander! Um... Is there anything I can help out with?
10600020.feeling5: Commander, you and everyone else here have taken such good care of me! When I'm with you, I feel relaxed, as if I'm back at home with Grammy! In return, please let me know if there's anything I can do for you!
10600020.unlock: Um... Are you the Commander? Oh, perfect! It's nice to meet you. My name is Honoka! I don't know how much I'll be able to help, but... let's be friends!
10600020.feeling4: Commander! I sent a letter to Grammy! I wrote that this is a fun place, with the Commander and many girls~ Hehehe~ Oh, next time, I'll show you around Grammy's place!
10600020.feeling1: Ughh... I just want to go back to my Grammy's place...
10600020.propose: Wh-what... Is it okay to give me something so valuable? I-I'll have to tell Grammy...! Um... I'll treasure this for all my life! Hehehe~
10600020.drop_descrip: Um... Are you the Commander? Oh, perfect! It's nice to meet you. My name is Honoka! I don't know how much I'll be able to help, but... let's be friends!
10600020.profile: An introduction? My name is Honoka. I love my Grammy! Also... I really like pro wrestling! I watch it on TV a lot and act out the scenes. I'm super good at imitations! The other day I broke my TV... Oh, um... promise me... you won't tell anyone.
10600020.touch2: Eep! Wh-whoa... There's a limit to what you can get away with, Commander!
10600020.mission: Missions? Do you do these everyday?
10600020.home: Commander, welcome back! Did anything interesting happen?
10600020.expedition: Commission complete~! Leave the rest to me~ I've helped Grammy out lots, so I'll be fine~
couple_encourage: Marie! Let's do our best!
Evil spirits, begone! Hehehe, is that how you do it~?
10600020.mail: There's some mail for you, Commander! I should write some mail to Grammy as well~
10600020.feeling3: Commander, won't you come shopping with me later? I want to buy some souvenirs for Grammy!
10600020.lose: Ohh~... I'm all out of energy~

305010.detail: Milord, shall we have tea together?
305010.touch: Milord, please rest your head here and allow me to clean your ears.
305010.login: Welcome back, Milord. Would you like to have your fortune told?
305010.battle: Milord, those who stand in your way shall find no mercy by my hand.
305010.feeling2: Milord, are you interested in the eight million gods of the Sakura Empire? It is fine if you aren't... I shall offer them your share of prayers.
305010.mission_complete: Milord, not claiming your rewards is a bad habit.
305010.main: I believe that we can change our misfortunes, as long as we work hard and pray...|I'll be happy as long as {namecode:79} has a chance to grow up.|My main gun specializes in heavy firepower, but is enough to shake my entire body! It can cause me some trouble, every now and then...
305010.feeling5: Milord, did you know that although a miko of the Sakura Empire must dedicate herself to the gods, she is not actually forbidden from romance? As a matter of fact, she is encouraged to find a husband in order to pass down traditions. Milord, what do you think about me?
305010.upgrade: Now, I can be of greater service to Milord.
305010.unlock: It is an honor to meet you. Milord, you must be the commander. I, {namecode:78}, have been waiting a long time for you. Surely, this is also the guidance of the gods. From now on, please allow me to serve youI
305010.feeling4: Kagura? That is a dance dedicated to the gods... Ah, why don't I perform just for you, milord? I would be embarrassed if others found out, so please keep it a secret between us, all right?
305010.feeling1: Milord, might you be the reincarnation of a god of calamity?
305010.propose: May our love last as long as the Great Pines in Takasago and the eternal Tsubaki. May we bring glory to our family, our name heard across the land. These words are said with my highest respect. With this, Milord, you and I become one. Though I may be inexperienced, let us care for and love each other for the rest of eternity.
305010.profile: I am the Sakura Empire's first super-dreadnought, {namecode:78}. In order to cleanse ourselves of the misfortune we were born with, my sister and I offer prayers to the gods every day. We will do whatever it takes to prevent another tragedy like Leyte Gulf from befalling us again. Milord, we would be most grateful should you lend us your aid.
305010.mission: Milord, a new mission is available. Please take a look.
305010.home: You've worked hard, Milord. Why don't you come to me and take a rest?
305010.win_mvp: May thy lost souls return home in peace.
305010.expedition: Milord, your girls have returned from commission. Shall we welcome them back together?
305010.mail: You have a new letter, milord. Please give it a look.
305010.feeling3: Milord, you seem exhausted as of late. Too much work is bad for your health. Please come with me, and allow me to purify you of your fatigue.
305010.lose: Oh no... has my ammunition storage been cursed again?

10600010.detail: Commander, what are we doing next?
10600010.login: Oh hello, Commander! Let's do our best today!
10600010.battle: Heheh, let the red rose of blood bloom forth!
10600010.feeling2: Wow, this place is huge... Lady Helena isn't here, so I feel a bit uneasy... No no, I'm an adult! I won't be shaken by something like this!
10600010.headtouch: Geez, please don't treat me like a little kid!
10600010.mission_complete: Mission complete! Am I a big help, Commander?
10600010.main: Yaaaaawn... I've gotten a bit sleepy...|Commander, do you feel tired? I can give you a massage!|Oh, Commander must be busy... Then I'll go play with Honoka first before coming back to help you! ...Ehh, I can't?
10600010.feeling5: I have a ton of fun being around you, Commander~ I'd love it if we could hang out more! ...Next time you're free, let's watch some horror movies together~
10600010.upgrade: Commander, do you feel like I've matured a bit?
10600010.unlock: Hello! Oh... What am I supposed to call you? "Commander"? Got it! My name is Marie Rose. Just call me Marie, okay? I'm counting on your support, Commander!
10600010.feeling4: Today I was invited to a tea party by girls from the Royal Navy, and we had a bunch of yummy princess cake! Heheh, I'm so happy to have made friends here!
10600010.feeling1: I hate you, I hate you, I hate you! If you keep this up, I'll only hate you even more!
10600010.propose: Heheh~ I've received something special from you~ I feel the same as you, Commander. Heheh, all of our memories together are precious treasures to me!
10600010.drop_descrip: Hello! Oh... What am I supposed to call you? "Commander"? Got it! My name is Marie Rose. Just call me Marie, okay? I'm counting on your support, Commander!
10600010.skill: I'll show you my real power!
10600010.profile: I'm the favorite servant of Lady Helena Douglas, head of DOATEC. I can clean, do laundry, cook, be a bodyguard, you name it, I can do it!
10600010.touch2: Where do you think you're touching me?!
10600010.mission: Commander, there are still missions that haven't been completed! You didn't forget, did you?
10600010.home: Oh, Commander! ...Ahem. Welcome back, Commander. You did a good job. Heheh~
10600010.win_mvp: Commander, did you see how useful I was?
10600010.expedition: Wow, there's so much stuff! Did you bring all of that back yourselves? Amazing!
couple_encourage: I'll protect you!
10600010.mail: Commander, it looks like there's some new mail waiting for you!
10600010.feeling3: There are so many amazing maids in the port! But I won't let them outdo me!
10600010.lose: I lost... What should I do, Commander...

101050.detail: Wow, look at that cutie! No, not me! The one over there!
101050.touch: Aaah, that tickles~! I can't keep the camera straight~
101050.login: Hey, Commander~ So listen, Sara's just soooo cute!
101050.battle: You over there! Strike a pose! I'm about to shoot~!
101050.feeling2: So, Commander, don't you wanna see some awesome photos of Saratoga? Fine, fine, I'll show you! Aren't I nice~
101050.mission_complete: The rewards are here~! Now we can buy new some film!
101050.main: I've got plenty of pictures of Sara. 800 bucks a print!|Mississippi will bring me back home just fine if I get lost!|Commander, have you seen Sara? I want to try my new camera!
101050.feeling5: Ah... You don't want to hear about Sara? You want... to know more about... me? Eh... um.... Ah! This is so embarrassing!
101050.upgrade: Now I can snap even more photos of Sara!
101050.unlock: Nice to meet you, Commander! I'm Gridley. I once escorted Saratoga~ She's such a cutie!
101050.feeling4: Look at this one. It's great, right? This one, too. I'm confident about this one. ...Commander, why are you looking at me instead of the photos?
101050.feeling1: You don't get to look at pictures of Sara anymore!
101050.propose: Commander, Commander! Strike a pose! 1... 2... 3! Cheese! ...That was a great shot! We'll get a copy each after we develop the film~
101050.drop_descrip: Gridley-class destroyer - Gridley, Hull Number DD-380!
101050.profile: I'm the first ship of the Gridley-class, and I was very active in the Pacific theater. But never mind that now, Commander. Want to look at photos of Sara?
101050.touch2: Commander! If you do that again, I'll photograph it and report it to the police~
101050.mission: The mission area is so pretty~ C'mon, let's go take some photos!
101050.home: I need to develop these photos~
101050.win_mvp: Ten out of ten! Commander, Commander! Take a photo of me too!
101050.expedition: The girls who went out on a commission are back. I wonder how the photos I asked for turned out?
101050.feeling3: Commander, didn't you promise we'd go see Sara together? What are we waiting for? Let's go!

10600030.detail: You call it the "Sakura Empire"? Somehow, it feels really familiar to me. Teehee~
10600030.login: Is it time to get to work, Commander? I will be right here, so tell me if you need anything.
10600030.battle: Teehee~ It's my time to shine. Let's get it done, everyone!
10600030.hp_warning: I'm not down for the count... just yet!
10600030.feeling2: These shipgirls also have sisters, I see... Both younger and older ones... Oh, sorry, I just had a random thought. Nothing to worry about.
10600030.mission_complete: Mission completed. That leaves us one less thing to worry about. Right, Commander?
10600030.main: Excuse me, but... what's a secretary supposed to do? My knowledge is bit spotty when it comes to these things...|You can see the sea from mostly anywhere here at the port. The scenery is truly gorgeous!|According to my fortune, today's destiny spot should be somewhere over...
10600030.feeling5: Um, Commander... Do you have a moment? I read my fortune today, and there's a so-called "destiny spot" in port. Could we... visit it, together? Oh, thank you so much! I'm sure fate has a surprise in store for us. Teehee~
10600030.upgrade: I feel more powerful... Thank you for that, Commander. Teehee~
10600030.unlock: Are you the Owner of the port? The "Commander"? Hello. My name is Kasumi, I'll be staying here for the foreseeable future. I hope we can both get along on friendly terms.
10600030.feeling4: My favorite food? Hmm... I suppose strawberry mille-feuilles. You don't think that's... childish, do you? I always worry that people will think that about me...
10600030.feeling1: Commander... I'm more than angry with you at this point. Reflect on your poor behavior.
10600030.propose: I can't believe you're offering something this precious to me... Teehee, I truly was destined to be at this port. Listen, um... I assume you don't mind, but I want stay here for a while longer. Teehee~
10600030.drop_descrip: Are you the Owner of the port? The "Commander"? Hello. My name is Kasumi, I'll be staying here for the foreseeable future. I hope we can both get along on friendly terms.
10600030.profile: I wonder how everyone's doing back at the Venus Islands... Oh, shoot! I'm supposed to be assisting you, and here I am letting my thoughts drift. My apologies, Commander.
10600030.touch2: Would you PLEASE show some self-restraint?!
10600030.mission: A new mission has come in. I could... give you a hand with it, if you'd so like?
10600030.home: I'm still learning how to use this so-called "rigging," but I try my best to do my part! Please put me on the next sortie, so I can prove myself.
10600030.expedition: Everyone working together to complete a commission... Yep, what a concept.
couple_encourage: Witness my Mugen Tenshin!
10600030.mail: Oh, there's new mail. Do you think it could be from your family, Commander?
10600030.feeling3: I see the Sakura Empire has its own disciples of ninjutsu... Hm? You wish to see mine? Err, I'm afraid... I can't do that. You aren't meant to openly show them to people.

10600050.detail: I can't believe there are so many girls at this port... You must have tricked them into coming here, didn't you?!
10600050.touch: Wh-what do you think you're doing, you dirty dog?!
10600050.login: Welcome back, Commander. ...You're quite the hard worker. Like a sled dog.
10600050.battle: If I have to do it, I'll do it properly. I just have to drive them away, right?
10600050.feeling2: Not just Misaki, but all of these other girls too... You dirty dog, what kind of devious schemes are you up to?!
10600050.mission_complete: You did this many missions on your own? My opinion of you has slightly improved... you silly dog.
10600050.main: Hey, you silly dog. This is a gift from someone. Apparently, there are some soufflé pancakes inside, too... I-I didn't say anything! Don't forget about it later!|You're quite a hard worker, which I'd say is good... Even for a lowly dog...|Hey, is there anything I can help you with? ...Don't take this the wrong way, I'm just doing this for leverage against you.
10600050.feeling5: Thanks for taking care of Misaki... I may have been wrong about you. You know, thinking that you were evil, and all. So... I'll watch you for a bit longer. That's fine, isn't it? You silly dog.
10600050.upgrade: Thank you... What? What's the problem with me saying "thanks" once in a while?!
10600050.unlock: Are you the person who led Misaki to this port? You go by the name... "Commander"? Hmm... I don't know how you sweet-talked her into it, but you're not fooling me. The moment you do anything strange... you better be on guard! My name? It's Nagisa. You... silly dog!
10600050.feeling4: Eh, you're saying you saw me talking to the sea? Oh, I'm a theater actor, so I was practicing... wait, you were spying on me?! You... You dirty dog!
10600050.propose: I-I understand your feelings! Geez, I'm not stupid like you are... My answer? D-don't you know without me telling you?! Like I always say, you're so slow, you silly dog! ...Hehe, I'll treasure this, you dog~
10600050.drop_descrip: Are you the person who led Misaki to this port? You go by the name... "Commander"? Hmm... I don't know how you sweet-talked her into it, but you're not fooling me. The moment you do anything strange... you better be on guard! My name? It's Nagisa. You... silly dog!
10600050.profile: Like I said the first time we met, I'm Misaki's sister, Nagisa. What I like most are soufflé pancakes, and what I hate most are green peppers. Do anything weird to Misaki, and I'll never forgive you for it, you dirty dog.
10600050.touch2: I guess... you really are an incorrigible dirty dog...
10600050.mission: Looks like there are still missions you haven't completed. Are you planning on doing them now, you silly dog?
10600050.home: Nice job in battle, you silly dog. But there's still a lot left for you to do, isn't there?
10600050.win_mvp: Whew, I'm a bit tired... I wonder if I overexerted myself.
10600050.expedition: Hey, you have girls back from a commission waiting for you out there. You silly dog.
couple_encourage: Misaki! Be careful! Make sure you don't get hurt!
Honoka, looks like you're wearing a shrine maiden's swimsuit as well!
10600050.mail: Here's some mail. Are you going senile? I can't believe you neglected it until I told you.
10600050.feeling3: If Misaki's having fun, it's fine, but... the moment you do anything weird, you'll regret it!
10600050.lose: It's all your fault, you silly dog...

10600040.detail: I get these weird vibes from this port and the shipgirls that live here... But most of all, I get them from you, Commander. Oh, I'm just messing with you! Ahaha!
10600040.touch: Yeees? Did you call for me, Commander?
10600040.login: Commander, hurry up~ Let's get to work, shall we?
10600040.battle: Aaaaall right! When you do something, you gotta do it right!
10600040.feeling2: So, I can drash across the ocean if I put this rigging on? The wonders of technology, huh!
10600040.headtouch: Hey, um... This feels odd to me...
10600040.mission_complete: Mission complete! Commander, don't forget to give me my share of the rewards! Oh, I'm just pulling your leg! Ahaha!
10600040.main: If you've got nothing else for me to do, I'm gonna head off to my part-time job... wait, I guess this is one, too...?|Mm~ I could go for some sweets right about now. Maybe a crêpe or something...|My sister might be scary at times, but she's a nice person at heart! ...Though, she might be a bit on the overprotective side...
10600040.feeling5: Commander, let's go to the dessert store~ Afterward, we can take a stroll together! I want to learn more about this place! And then, after that... um... Well, let's just get going!
10600040.upgrade: What do you think? Can you feel my growth?
10600040.unlock: It's nice to meet you! From what I've heard, you're the "Commander," right? I'm Misaki. I have experience with various part-time jobs, so... I'm confident that I can be of help to you all. Let's do our best!
10600040.feeling4: Apparently, there's a two-for-one deal at the store for bubble milk tea right now! Two might be a bit too much for me, though... Commander, if you're free, do you want to go with me?
10600040.feeling1: This port might be an interesting place, but you? You're not very dependable... I guess the responsibility for whipping you into shape falls on me, the part-timer~
10600040.propose: Ever since I've arrived at this place, you've taken such good care for me. I can't believe that I'm about to receive something this precious from you... Thank you, Commander! I'll work even harder for you!
10600040.drop_descrip: It's nice to meet you! From what I've heard, you're the "Commander," right? I'm Misaki. I have experience with various part-time jobs, so... I'm confident that I can be of help to you all. Let's do our best!
10600040.profile: You want me to introduce myself? I'm Misaki, and my hobbies include scuba diving, stargazing, and... reading comics, I guess. Also, I really like mango vanilla crêpes and bubble milk tea! Oh, right, and... be nice to my sister, Nagisa!
10600040.touch2: Wah?! Geez, I'll be really angry if you do that again!
10600040.mission: Commander, you've got new missions! Don't we get rewards for completing them?
10600040.home: Oh, Commander, nice work on that last battle! Now, how about a short break?
10600040.win_mvp: We won! Woohoo, a V for victory!
10600040.expedition: The commission team's returned! I wonder if they brought back some sweets~
couple_encourage: Sis? Oh, never mind...
I can take care of myself, so focus on yourself, sis!
10600040.mail: Commander, you've got mail. Come take a look!
10600040.feeling3: Everyone looks extraordinary when fighting, but I guess they're really just normal girls when they're not. I've even found some friends who like comic books, heheh.
10600040.lose: We lost... I can't believe it...

103160.detail: What you can do, what you should do, and what you will do – the choices one must make. You, however, need only focus on what you do best, Commander.
103160.touch: Could you fetch me an Oxy-cola? Thanks... Ahhh! That hits the spot!
103160.login: Okay! Let's get to work, Commander!
103160.feeling2: As long as the will do to right exists, people will live righteously even without being ordered to. I pray that you will stay on the path of justice, Commander.
103160.mission_complete: There's our mission rewards. Good to have the money for retrofits and repairs.
103160.main: I'll get this work done in good time. I mean, that's what you should expect of your subordinate, Commander.|SHE'S Quincy?! L-looks pretty different from the one I know... But I guess it's not that unusual for ships to share the same name.|Power alone won't fundamentally solve all one's problems. This should go without saying, Commander, but please try to remember this fact.
103160.feeling5: Man... I doubt I'll ever get used to this... Maybe I should act more girly when... No, this is a me-problem, not a you-problem! ... *Sigh*, I can't think straight when you're around, Commander...
103160.upgrade: Great! I'm getting fitter and fitter.
103160.unlock: Heya. Are you in need of help? I'm Baltimore, a heavy cruiser just passing by... Okay, that's enough jokes for now... Baltimore, awaiting your orders, Commander.
103160.feeling4: You want to go shopping with me? Sure, consider it done. You wanna make a date out of it? I mean, might as... H-hold on! When you say "date," you mean THAT kind of date?!
103160.feeling1: Commander, you ought to open your heart a little.
103160.propose: Yes, I vow to be with you through thick and thin, and to love and to cherish for all my life, Commander. ... So, uh, once you put the ring on my fing– W-what is it? Hey, what're you doing?! Ah, ahh...
103160.drop_descrip: Baltimore-class heavy cruiser – Baltimore, Hull Number CA-68.
103160.skill: We've got an opening... Let's take 'em out!
103160.profile: I'm Baltimore, the lead ship of my class of CAs. I was the first CA to be designed and constructed without the limitations of any naval treaties, thanks to which I could equip cutting-edge weaponry for the time. And within this fleet, I will fight for justice and freedom.
103160.touch2: Eek?! ... Y-you did not just hear that, got it?!
103160.mission: Missions, missions. Let's start by checking the list.
103160.win_mvp: You crooks should've used your powers for good.
103160.expedition: Commission complete. I could use some exercise, so could you let me have the next one?
couple_encourage: Wichita, don't go overboard, now!
Got a feeling like we'll make a good team!
103160.mail: You've got a message, Commander. I really think you should check these more often.
103160.feeling3: Let's not be overly formal and get to it: what do you wanna do next? I'm open to chat about pretty much whatever, so if anything's on your mind, just tell me.
103160.lose: Even the good guys face setbacks sometimes...

10600070.detail: High-stakes gamble are once-a-day only! You'll have to wait until tomorrow to give the wheel another spin, Commander.
10600070.touch: This next gamble wiiiill... have to wait until our work is finished!
10600070.login: Greetings, Commander. What do you say to... a small bet before starting work?
10600070.battle: Heheh, I'm the wild card in this battle!
10600070.feeling2: This one time, I saw someone do a "straight up" bet with all their chips. You just have to admire the moxie it takes to bet against Lady Luck like that!
10600070.headtouch: Heheh. Is there something the matter?
10600070.mission_complete: Mission done on time and with flying colors. You might have it in you to be a casino manager, Commander!
10600070.main: Which do you prefer, Commander? Skill-based card games, or luck-based roulette?|You can wager more than just chips. Like an afternoon teatime, for instance. The loser provides the tea and biscuits!|Something... on your mind? I could offer you some insight, if you'd like. Assuming you win this next bet, that is!
10600070.feeling5: I really do like gambling with you, Commander. Win or lose, it's lots of fun! That's your biggest charm point, in fact. Heheh!
10600070.upgrade: The house advantage grows ever so slightly!
10600070.unlock: Are you the one in charge here? The "Commander"? I'm Monica, the dealer! Well, dealer-in-training. I know it's sudden, but would you care to gamble with me? The stakes will, of course, be high!
10600070.feeling4: Are you the type that's easily influenced by pretty girls, Commander? That's not good! You need be focused at all times, or you won't win.
10600070.feeling1: You can't give up after losing just one single bet, Commander. Life, as we all know, is one big series of wins and losses!
10600070.propose: Huh? You're giving THIS to ME? Can I really have it? Talk about the bet of a lifetime... Heheh, I'll call your wager! Or would you rather I raise it?
10600070.drop_descrip: Are you the one in charge here? The "Commander"? I'm Monica, the dealer! Well, dealer-in-training. I know it's sudden, but would you care to gamble with me? The stakes will, of course, be high!
10600070.profile: Why do I want to be a dealer? Because it's cool! Why else? Dealer distribute cards with so much style, and they've got such solid poker faces!
10600070.touch2: Th-there's no sleight of hand going on here!
10600070.mission: Hey, Commander, you've got unfinished business! Let's wrap things up so we can gamble!
10600070.home: Way to go, Commander. Here, a glass of water. Heheh, a dealer needs to keep an eye on the player, don't you know?
10600070.win_mvp: Heheh! There are no backsies in gambling!
10600070.expedition: A commission team has returned! It was a gamble, but those lucky girls won!
couple_encourage: Heheh! Would you like to bet on this battle?
10600070.mail: Don't forget your mail now, Commander!
10600070.feeling3: Heheh, let me show you this dealing method I learned a while back, Commander!
10600070.lose: Dammiiiiit! Next time, I swear it... Next time!

502041.detail: Chao Ho thinks up the couplets, and I write them down. Don't you think we make a good team? Besides, seeing Chao Ho's brows furrow in thought is super cute... Anyway, let's think up some lines together later.
502041.touch: Since it's the Spring Festival, how about taking a break?
502041.login: The warmth of spring often lulls many into oversleeping... But, Commander, it seems like you're accustomed to waking up early?
502041.main: Miss Yat Sen, I'll help you prepare the food for tonight's reunion dinner. What about the fish? I'll start it up if you'd like.|I never thought I'd be able to enjoy the company of my sister and all our friends like this... Yes, it's all thanks to you, Commander.|Fu Shun, if you throw any more firecrackers into the pond... I'll change your seat to be right next to that lotus~♪
502041.unlock: Happy New Year, Commander. I've come to deliver you blessings for this coming year... Next, you're going to ask for a red envelope, right? Hehe, just teasing~
502041.drop_descrip: Happy New Year, Commander. I've come to deliver you blessings for this coming year... Next, you're going to ask for a red envelope, right? Hehe, just teasing~
502041.touch2: The excitement of the festival seems to have gone to your head. Hehe~
502041.home: In the warm spring breeze, snow melts and life blooms anew. Spring is the season of life.
502041.win_mvp: A~ job~ well~ done~♪ ...Hehe, did you like that?

10600060.detail: Well, well. What shall I do for amusement now... Have you any good ideas?
10600060.touch: Are you planning on checking my body yourself? Hehe, how daring.
10600060.login: Just arriving, Commander? Heheh, you will show me around the port, won't you?
10600060.battle: Disrupting my vacation like this... I hope you're ready for what's coming. Hehehe.
10600060.hp_warning: The battle is just starting, is it not?
10600060.feeling2: One year for a human is no time at all to a Tengu. ...However, that does not mean I have no interest in the world of you humans.
10600060.mission_complete: You seem to have completed your tasks. Hehehe, are you tired? Go ahead and rest awhile.
10600060.main: In order to fly, humans created airplanes... I wonder how the view from within one is?|I'd like to drink some tea while snacking on some manjuu... Not those little ones you have here, mind you. Ah-haha.|There is a strange presence within the ranks of the Sakura Empire. Hehehe, interesting, how very interesting...
10600060.feeling5: Oh, we're on a "date"? It seems I was taking you far too lightly, hehehe. Well, what kinds of events should I look forward to?
10600060.upgrade: Haha, that's not enough. Give me more...♥
10600060.unlock: Oh? You don't seem to fear me... Who might you be? ...I see, so it is you who rules over this place. Then I shall call you "Commander." I am Nyotengu. You would do best to keep me entertained, hehe.
10600060.feeling4: No matter where I go, humans seem to love festivals and feasts just the same. Ah-ha-ha... That's right, I love them too♥
10600060.feeling1: You... You are a boring human...
10600060.propose: To think you'd try to detain me in the world of man, what inconceivable rubbish... Ah-ha-ha, that was merely a joke. My vacation is still in its youth. I shall stay by your side for the moment's passing♥
10600060.drop_descrip: Oh? You don't seem to fear me... Who might you be? ...I see, so it is you who rules over this place. Then I shall call you "Commander." I am Nyotengu. You would do best to keep me entertained, hehe.
10600060.skill: Haha, what a trifle you are!
10600060.profile: I am undoubtedly a tengu. Oh? If you have any doubts, why not confirm it with those eyes and hands? Ah-haha...♥
10600060.mission: There are still duties left for you to do. What a forgetful one, hehehe.
10600060.home: After battle comes official duties, it seems. You must be suffering, so I shall lend you a hand.
10600060.expedition: Your subordinates are calling for you. You shouldn't keep a woman waiting for long.
couple_encourage: Haha, I shall show you the power of these "carrier-based aircraft" of mine
Oh, what a curious fate it is that ties us together.
10600060.mail: "May-ull"? I am most curious as to where it came from.
10600060.feeling3: This port abounds with curious "take-knowledge-ease." Commander, might I ask for a tour? Hehehe, you know quite a bit, don't you?
10600060.lose: To corner me like so... One must always be on their guard...

201032.detail: I'm the Dungeon Master Bunny! Ehehe, it's a refreshing twist on a classic theme, right?
201032.touch: Do you have a question about the rules? Heheh~ Allow me to teach you what you need to know~
201032.login: Welcome, Commander. What would you like to play today? A casual party game, or something more strategic?
201032.main: Mmhmm, Glorious, all you have to do is toss this D20.|Err, wait a sec, what does the rulebook say...? ...Sorry, there's still a lot I need to learn.|Um... Commander, it's your turn. Goodness, please stop spacing out already~!
201032.unlock: Welcome to Ardent's game house~! I'm here to provide fun and excitement for everyone as the GM– ...Ehehe, actually, I'm still learning as a play~♪
201032.drop_descrip: Welcome to Ardent's game house~! I'm here to provide fun and excitement for everyone as the GM– ...Ehehe, actually, I'm still learning as a play~♪
201032.touch2: Hauuu?! Y-you didn't do that on purpose... did you?
201032.home: I brought juice for everyone! No need to be shy, Commander~♪
201032.lose: There's going to be a penalty round for sure now...

305012.detail: Milord, I feel my bad luck melting away when I am with you... Thank you very much.
305012.touch: You'd like to take me out? Are you sure? Um, in that case... there are a lot of places I'd like to go with you. Ehehe~
305012.login: Milord, I just made some snacks. Would you like to try some?
305012.feeling2: "Dating" is such an incredible word. Milord, even though I've become accustomed to living with you, my heart skips a beat every time I hear that word...
305012.main: Ah... oh no, look at the time... Milord, time passes so quickly when I'm with you. I forgot that I was supposed to take Yamashiro shopping... |Milord, do you know how to play Hanafuda cards? Ah, was it Souryuu who taught you how to play? Um, in that case... shall we play together? |Milord, the freshly washed blankets sure smell nice. Surely, they'll also be very comfortable to sleep on.
305012.feeling5: Milord, being able to spend every day with you like this makes it almost feel like we're a married couple... Ah, um, please forget I said anything!
305012.unlock: Being able to wait for my beloved in this homely attire... Milord, my life has changed so much since meeting you. *giggle*
305012.feeling4: Milord, I have a small request... but please promise not to laugh. I've always been jealous of the way Akashi jumps into your arms like a spoiled child, but... it's a bit embarrassing to ask... so, um...
305012.feeling1: Milord, have you grown tired of me...?
305012.drop_descrip: Being able to wait for my beloved in this homely attire... Milord, my life has changed so much since meeting you. *giggles*
305012.mission: Milord, I believe it's time to complete your missions. I shall accompany you.
305012.home: Milord, the last battle must have been very strenuous, yes? In that case, please come lie down and rest for a while.
305012.win_mvp: Milord, I treasure the time I spend with you above all else.
305012.mail: Milord, I have brought the mail.

407031.detail: The sands of time pile up to become a mountain; The passing of time eventually becomes history. Hehehe, how interesting.
407031.touch: The plan already takes the holidays into account. There won't be a problem even if you take some time off to rest, Officer.
407031.login: So you're working over the holidays. How commendable of you.
407031.main: I hear this is the time of year when New Year's gifts are handed out. Officer, would you rather be the one handing out the gifts or receiving them?|Eugen, Heinrich, there's a limit to how much rucku... teasing you should do.|Graf Zeppelin, why don't you try studying the Sakura Empire's shrines? Even if you don't pay your respects to their gods, the Sakura Empire's amazake seems quite interesting.
407031.unlock: Eugen, you said that this was is a ceremonial outfit from the Sakura Empire? Surprisingly, it does seem to suit me rather well. Oh, I'm supposed to offer my well-wishes for the New Year at this time, yes?
407031.drop_descrip: Eugen, you said that this was is a ceremonial outfit from the Sakura Empire? Surprisingly, it does seem to suit me rather well. Oh, I'm supposed to offer my well-wishes for the New Year at this time, yes?
407031.touch2: Officer, are you telling me that this much is enough for you to not be able to hold back?
407031.home: Go take a break, and leave the deliberation to me. It's not yet time for you to make your appearance, Officer.
407031.expedition: The commissions have been completed. Please leave their reception to me. There's no need for you to waste your time, Officer.

502040.detail: Going by launch date, one could say that I am actually Chao Ho's older sister... But alas, since she wants that role so badly, she can have it. Besides, being the "little sister" comes with perks of its own. Hehe~♪
502040.touch: If you're tired, you should go ahead and rest. Collapsing due to overwork is inefficient.
502040.login: The ever-industrious commander, right on time today. Hey... have you seriously never thought about playing hooky?
502040.battle: Purge all evil. Become as a stalwart blade.
502040.hp_warning: We will not, cannot, back down here...!
502040.feeling2: Chao Ho should be doing her usual training just about now. Commander, why don't we go take a little field trip? Hehe~
502040.headtouch: If you mess up my hair, I'll have you style it for me for a week starting tomorrow, you hear?
502040.mission_complete: Mission complete. Now, if I could just enjoy a meal, soak in the bath, and then get into bed... that would be the life. Hehe~
502040.main: Chao Ho, if you want to be seen as the big sister, you're going to have to do things yourself instead of relying on the commander. Heehee~♪|Reminder from Ying Swei~ You've had your head in the clouds for a while~|Are you interested in the Four Treasures of the Study? I'd be glad to instruct you. Hehe, not to boast, but I'm quite confident in my abilities.
502040.feeling5: There are a lot of things I'd like to say to you, but whenever I'm in front of you, it's like the words just won't come out... I'm afraid I'll have to write my feelings out for you, so please don't laugh.
502040.upgrade: Indeed. You must be strong if you wish to protect what is dear to you.
502040.unlock: It is a pleasure to meet you, Commander. I am the elder of the Chao Ho sisters, Ying Swei. Hmm, Chao Ho said that she's the big sister? Hmm, I guess you're not as gullible as she is. Hehe~♪
502040.feeling4: "Whenever I'm with the commander, I get all excited and can't figure out why... but, but..." Oh, ahem... I'd appreciate it if you could act like I was just talking to myself.
502040.feeling1: ...I have nothing to say to you.
502040.propose: Ink does not fade with the passage of time... I wrote my feelings down with the hope that they also may never fade. I now offer these words to you, along with myself.
502040.drop_descrip: Chao Ho-class protected cruiser – Ying Swei.
502040.profile: I am the second ship of the Chao Ho-class protected cruisers, Ying Swei. I'm also Chao Ho's sister. By the way, if you see the two of us bickering, don't be alarmed. It's nothing more than our way of expressing affection for one another. Hehe~♪
502040.touch2: Wouldn't it be a great time for me to tell everyone how much of a pervert you are? If you want me to reconsider, you'll have to make me a little promise first. Hehe~
502040.mission: Commander, we've got new missions. If Chao Ho was here, I'm sure she'd be nagging you to kingdom come. Hehe~
502040.home: I'm sure there are a lot of things you're dying to tell me. But that can wait until after you've rested up.
502040.win_mvp: I'll wait until I get back before declaring victory.
502040.expedition: The expedition fleet is back. Don't forget to reward all our hardworking friends.
couple_encourage: Sister, don't let the enemy get away with underestimating us.
Let's do this, together!
502040.mail: You've got new mail... You know, stone-cold printed text doesn't have that same human touch as something handwritten.
502040.feeling3: Chao Ho has been complaining to you that I've been pushing my chores onto her, hasn't she? Don't listen to her. I've just been instructing my little sister, who has stubbornly been running away from her responsibilities, about the realities of being an adult. Hehe~
502040.lose: Do I not have enough power... to stop the enemy's advance?

900007.detail: Fate can be easily derailed, Commander.
900007.login: Welcome back. Shall we have tea before getting back to work?
900007.battle: Acts of bravery beget success... All ships, open fire!
900007.hp_warning: Get up! We're looking for a fight!
900007.feeling2: I heard that my current name was chosen because my original one could bring misfortune, but... judging by how things turned out... it seems I'm unable to escape my fate...
900007.main: Expensive isn't always better, but it's your job to maximize our combat capability, Commander.|I don't want to suffer the pain of losing comrades...|Would you like to have some tea? I have a sandwich as well. I'm a big fan of pickles, you know!
900007.feeling5: I had a dream, a dream of that time which makes me feel hopeless even now... But when I open my eyes and see you by my side, it feels like life... like life isn't so bad after all...
900007.unlock: You're the Commander? Very well. I, Prince of Wales, shall let you witness my true strength.
900007.feeling4: Fighting with honor is my motto. I wish it could be the same when it comes to love. So... can you stay with me a bit longer? I have something important to tell you, Commander...
900007.feeling1: Keep your distance. You are not qualified to command me...
900007.propose: To me, the ritual isn't as important as the fact that you've already recognized our love... However, receiving such a wonderful gift still makes me happy. Thank you, Commander... I'll keep this with me forever!
900007.drop_descrip: King George V-class battleship, Prince of Wales. Hull Number 53.
900007.profile: I'm the second ship of the King George V-class battleships, the Prince of Wales. I once escorted the Prime Minister to sign the Atlantic Charter. I turned a new page in the history books of weaponry? Hmph, how dare you mention that in front of me.
900007.touch2: You know what this touch means, don't you?
900007.mission: It's time to test your resolve, Commander.
900007.home: Sometimes victories come down to nothing but luck. Don't get too full of yourself, Commander.
900007.win_mvp: Success is gratifying every single time.
900007.expedition: Commissions complete! Please welcome the fleet home.
900007.mail: You have a new message, Commander.
900007.feeling3: You never know how many plans, hopes, and efforts would sink into the sea with you, Commander. Don't die too easily.
900007.lose: A horse may stumble even though he has four legs. Let's try again next time.

900006.detail: The pride of the Royal Navy, admire as you wish.
900006.touch: Appropriate contact is indeed essential, shall we dance?
900006.login: Welcome back, Commander. Care for a cup of tea?
900006.feeling2: Commander, it's such a great afternoon, shall we have a chat? ...Hm, alright, I'll talk about the times when I was with Renown.
900006.mission_complete: Glory comes with reward, do not forget the latter.
900006.main: An outstanding commander must have an in-depth knowledge of tea.|This word is... ah, so I read it wrong. Sorry, my vision isn't very sharp.|Listen more, speak less. You should listen to others' opinions, but retain your own judgments.
900006.feeling5: Shall I compare thee to a summer day? Thou art more lovely and more temperate... So long as I can breathe, or eyes can see, so long lives this poem, and this gives life to thee... A beautiful verse, could Commander read this for me?
900006.unlock: Greetings, Commander. As the pride of the Royal Navy, Hood comes with victory.
900006.feeling4: Hm? Too close? While a lady must be elegant, they take the initiative towards their love, you know?
900006.feeling1: Sigh, seems like you have to learn it the hard way.
900006.propose: Haha, you cannot express your feelings to a lady this nervously. But your feelings have reached my heart... it is Hood's pleasure.
900006.skill: Elegant, but not breakable like a vase!
900006.profile:
Indeed, the pride of the Royal Navy stands before you.
To be refined at all times is the upbringing of a royalty. The Denmark Strait? Victory and defeat are commonplace among those who fight. That was but a single failure.
900006.touch2: Commander should know very well the consequences of disrespecting a lady... are you prepared?
900006.mission: Commander, you've got a new mission. Take a look, would you?
900006.home: Commander, is the tea ready? Let's taste it while we review.
900006.win_mvp: The warm sun, the cool breeze, a brilliant victory.
900006.expedition: Completing commissions is also a show of honor, will you not treat those children?
couple_encourage: prestige, do not wander again
keep the Etiquette, counterattack
at your service, Your Majesty
Go ahead, we are Royal Glory
900006.mail: It's unopened... Commander, it's not gentlemanly to ignore messages from others, you know?
900006.feeling3: I talk about being refined at all times, but Commander need not to force yourself to comply. Your normal self is most charming.
900006.lose: Victory and defeat are commonplace among those who fight, and we have all the time in the world.

502035.detail: Just like Ning Hai's, me and the girls made my cake with love. It's a chao ji da strawberry cake... I wonder how many days it would take for me to eat by myself...? Hehehe.
502035.touch: Ning Hai told me to pass out my cake without bothering the Commander!
502035.login: Here's your cake. Eat up. Ning Hai is passing out blueberry cake, but I've got strawberry.
502035.main: Baobao, where do I bring the next slice...?|There's going to be so much good stuff at the party... Commander, they have to have some baozi, don't they?!|Ning Hai always says I need to make more friends... But really I have so many friends already!
502035.unlock: There's always a lot of delicious food at these parties! But, my sister said I'm not allowed to have any cake until everyone's gotten their slice... Baobao, let's be on our best behavior!
502035.drop_descrip: There's always a lot of delicious food at these parties! But, my sister said I'm not allowed to have any cake until everyone's gotten their slice... Baobao, let's be on our best behavior!
502035.touch2: Mm. I've known for a long time, my sister and I are very different in that department.
502035.home: I'm... so hungry... Maybe just a little bite... No! Ning Hai told me not to!

305023.detail: Banquets are a lot of fun! Next time, we should have a Sakura-style banquet and invite everyone from the other camps!
305023.touch: Milord, Milord, I hear that there will be dancing at the banquet! Would it be okay for me to dance with you?
305023.login: Heheh~♪ Going to a banquet with Milord... Hawawa?! Milord, how long have you been standing there?
305023.main: Milord, Milord, what's this? And this? There are so many things I haven't experienced before, my head's spinning! |Milord, are you sure you'd like to take someone like me to the banquet...? I won't make you look bad, right? |Shigure, don't do anything weird at the banquet. You'll bother the others!
305023.feeling5: Milord, Milord, you've done so much for me, so is there anything I can do for you...? Whatever you want, I-I'll do it!
305023.unlock: Fusou told me that I have to wear a Western-style dress to the banquet, so she got one for me! Milord, Milord, isn't this dress pretty?
305023.drop_descrip: Fusou told me that I have to wear a Western-style dress to the banquet, so she got one for me! Milord, Milord, isn't this dress pretty?
305023.touch2: M-Milord! It's going to be troublesome if everyone sees us!

202150.detail: Commander, is there anything I can help you with regarding equipment?
202150.touch: Commander, want to take a break and come water the flowers with me?
202150.login: My name symbolises the break of dawn. Ehehe~ Do you feel more energetic from seeing me?
202150.battle: May we be blessed with victory~
202150.hp_warning: Light of dawn, illuminate our path...!
202150.feeling2: Commander, would you like to see the roses that I planted? I have a lot of different kinds~
202150.mission_complete: Some mission rewards had not yet been collected, so I retrieved them in your stead.
202150.main: Eastern Radiance? Oh, it's a great place. Mm... for example... |Even though I don't mind if you stare at me, please do your work properly~ |Hold still, Commander, there's something stuck on your cheek... There! Now, please do your best at work~
202150.feeling5: Lately, some girls have been grumbling that I've been monopolosing all your time... But, I'm not going to back down on this. Commander, you too should be prepared to deal with a bunch of sulking girls~
202150.upgrade: Commander, I'll be able to help with even more things now~
202150.unlock: Greetings, Commander. I am the fourth ship of the Arethusa-class light cruisers, Aurora. From now on, I shall serve as your secretary. Please feel free to ask anything of me~
202150.feeling4: Commander, come here for a moment~ ... Hehe, this rose suits you best after all! Eh? I'm not making fun of you... In that case, why don't you pick one out to put on me? I'm sure I'll love whatever you pick~
202150.feeling1: Commander, please refrain from making a fool of yourself in public.
202150.propose: "A rose by any name would smell as sweet." Whether I am called Aurora, the "Goddess of Dawn," or even Chongqing, I am still the same me. Yes... I will always be at your side.
202150.drop_descrip: Arethusa-class light cruiser - Aurora, pennant number 12
202150.skill: Commander, helping you solve problems and leave worries behind is also part of my job~
202150.profile: I am Aurora of the Royal Navy, fourth ship of the Arethusa-class. You are welcome to call me the "Goddess of Dawn," but please forget any nasty-sounding nicknames you might hear like the "Silver Phantom." Commander, perhaps you are familiar with some of the other names that I've been called?
202150.touch2: Commander! I... I'm going to be mad! Jeez! I'll really get mad!
202150.mission: Commander, a new mission dossier has been issued. I have already highlighted the most important parts, so please look over it.
202150.home: Good work. Please take some time to relax.
202150.expedition: Commander, it will be a problem if you keep staring at me and forget about the girls who have returned from commission.
couple_encourage: Ping Hai, Ning Hai, are you two also practicing mask-changing opera? Eh, you're doing it to make money...?
If you can't decide, how about consulting a rose?
202150.mail: There's new mail, shall I read it aloud for you?
202150.feeling3: The goddess, Aurora, was said to have "rose-coloured fingers." Though the same can't be said for me, my fingers at least smell like roses. Commander, want to check for yourself?
202150.lose: It seems I have not yet become accustomed to the battlefield...

502034.detail: Big sister made a stupidly jam-packed schedule. Just looking at it makes me sleepy... But there's apparently lots of tasty food by the tourist attractions, so I'm coming along!
502034.touch: The goal of our vacation? Mine is to try *all* of the Sakura Empire's yummiest food!
502034.login: Commander, I wanna try the Sakura Empire's take on ramen!
502034.main: Big sister said this is a prize vacation, so we can't try out all the local restaurants... What even is a "prize vacation"?|Big sister looks thrilled to get to enjoy a vacation! Seeing her smile, and getting to eat so much good food, has me feeling thrilled too!|Let go of my jacket, big sister~! I've not finished my food yet! Give it a try you too, it's really yummy!
502034.unlock: The Sakura Empire has lots of delicious food that I've never tried before! Yeah! It's a great place!
502034.drop_descrip: The Sakura Empire has lots of delicious food that I've never tried before! Yeah! It's a great place!
502034.mission: There's so much tasty food I want to try!
502034.home: Commander, I wanna eat some tempura!

305022.touch: Merry Christmas! I've already wrapped up a lot of presents! Milord, would you like to pick one out?
305022.main: I sprained my ankle on accident... Uuu... Milord, can you help me massage it? |Milord, milord, when it's New Years... will you come see my sister and me perform Kagura? |Woah... Milord, milord, it's a snowy Christmas!
305022.unlock: Merry Christmas! Milord, milord, how do I look? Is my Christmas outfit pretty? Ehehe~ Big sis also praised me today!
305022.drop_descrip: Merry Christmas! Milord, milord, how do I look? Is my Christmas outfit pretty? Ehehe~ Big sis also praised me today!
305022.touch2: Milord... that's not the spot I sprained!

101051.touch: What's in this bag? Guhehe~ an album of premium Saratoga photos! As long as I have this, she will always be at my side!
101051.main: Christmas special edition Saratoga photos, one thousand dollars each! Guhehe~ my fangirl power level increases during the holiday season! |Commander, can you take some photos of me with Saratoga? |Thanks for the waterproof camera, Commander! I'll be sure to take good care of it!
101051.unlock: Commander, Merry Christmas! Guhehe~ Won't you attend my "Super Special Sexy Sara (tentative)" photoshoot event?
101051.drop_descrip: Commander, Merry Christmas! Guhehe~ Won't you attend my "Super Special Sexy Sara (tentative)" photoshoot event?

103161.detail: Do you know how to get to my clubroom? Or should I show you the way?
103161.touch: Oh, my uniform's completely soaked... T-thanks for letting me know...
103161.main: Our club is mainly for having fun, so anyone can join. You should join a club you'd like too, Commander.|Yo, Cleveland! Up for another round of basketball later? You bring Independence and I'll get Pittsburgh on the team!|A drink? Sure, I could use one! ... Ahh, that's the ticket!
103161.unlock: Oh, you wanna observe my club activities, Commander? Ahah, as you can tell, it's just a sports club with the goal of making you sweat. Nothing suspicious about that, is there...?
103161.drop_descrip: Oh, you wanna observe my club activities, Commander? Ahah, as you can tell, it's just a sports club with the goal of making you sweat. Nothing suspicious about that, is there...?
103161.home: Looks like you worked up a good sweat. Here, a towel. Should I go get a drink for you, too?

305025.detail: Ehehe... If I bottle up some of the fresh air here, everyone back at port will get to experience the atmosphere here as well!
305025.login: The beach here isn't quite like the one back at the port, but it's totally beautiful! Ehehe, I'm so glad I got to go on a vacation with you, Milord!
305025.main: Look, Milord, someone's surfing over there!|How are we supposed to bring all these bottles back to port? ...Milord, I'm sure you'll think up an idea!|There are tons of fun places other than the beach? Mmhmm, I'll gladly accompany you, Milord!
305025.unlock: Woah, even the air tastes totally different at this vacation spot! Milord, Milord, um, Akashi asked me to bottle up some of the air here for her! Want to give me a hand?
305025.drop_descrip: Woah, even the air tastes totally different at this vacation spot! Milord, Milord, um, Akashi asked me to bottle up some of the air here for her! Want to give me a hand?
305025.touch2: Waah! ...I'm so sorry, Milord, I just swung a bottle at you, didn't I...?
305025.home: Milord, Milord, if you're tired, why not take a little break under that umbrella?

202151.detail: My outfit is a bit surprising? Ehehe, from now on, you'll learn more and more about a different side of me~
202151.touch: Eh? What's the matter? Ah, I was just thinking... it'd be great if things could stay like this next year, and the year after that, and forever more...
202151.login: Commander, welcome back. Please take your time, I only just got here myself.
202151.main: Commander, would you like to eat hotpot? If you're not good with spice, I'll prepare a two-sided pot~|If you're tired, why don't you enjoy a mandarin while listening to me read a story?
202151.unlock: I have long prepared for this day... Commander, would you like to listen to my storytelling?
202151.drop_descrip: I have long prepared for this day... Commander, would you like to listen to my storytelling?

502036.detail: Commander, let's take these pandas back to port! ...We're not allowed? Aww...
502036.touch: I'm not allowed to feed them baozi? Okay, I'll keep that in mind...
502036.login: Big sister told me to look after these pandas! Does that mean I should play with them?
502036.main: Look at the camera! I'm gonna take a group photo!|Do you wanna pet the pandas too, Commander?|Eat lots, Baobao! Then you'll grow up to be as big as your buddy!
502036.unlock: Cheese! That came out looking good! Hehehe~ I'm really glad to be a part of this charity event for nature, along with you and my sister! Baobao is really glad too!
502036.drop_descrip: Cheese! That came out looking good! Hehehe~ I'm really glad to be a part of this charity event for nature, along with you and my sister! Baobao is really glad too!
502036.home: I'm gonna take a bunch of pics of these cute pandas and show them to people around the port!

805011.detail: Iris' teachings do not go as far as to forbid its followers from spreading their wings. Let us enjoy today with everyone to our heart's content. Consider this as yet another of Heaven's many blessings.
805011.touch: My... Where are you taking me, Commander?
805011.login: Scenery that calms the heart... Commander, you've got good taste.
805011.main: Commander, I'll be heading to the beach for a bit. ... Hehe. Indeed, this is a bit different from how I am usually. Would you like to come along with me? | Frozen treats are most effective against hot and humid weather like this... Shall we ask Dunkerque to prepare some more next time? | Jean Bart... Perhaps it's better to spend some more time with her... Sigh... |nil|nil
805011.feeling5: Walking together on the beach like this while basking our ears in the sounds of the sea... Agréable. Hehehe, this is quite a rare experience. Commander ... Thanks for being with me. I'll cherish this moment.
805011.unlock: This swimsuit... Yes, the one Émile picked out for me, seems a bit skimpy... I didn't think she'd be the type to trick me into wearing something like this, but... Commander, where are you looking?
805011.drop_descrip: This swimsuit... Yes, the one Émile picked out for me, seems a bit skimpy... I didn't think she'd be the type to trick me into wearing something like this, but... Commander, where are you looking?
805011.touch2: If you know what's good for you, I wouldn't assume that a girl is defenseless just because she's in a swimsuit.
805011.home: I don't wish for my absence to become a burden on you, Commander. If there's anything I can help with, please let me know.
805011.expedition: We have a really good view from up here. I can even see a commission group starting to return out there.

303040.touch: Commander, did you also come to wind down with some light stretching?
303040.login: Welcome back, Commander! Did you get enough to eat? If you're still hungry, I can cook something for you!
303040.battle: Everyone! Stay alert, protect yourself, and don't be reckless!
303040.feeling2: Did you clean your room, Commander? Did you lock the door? Have you forgotten anything?
303040.mission_complete: Commander, leaving your rewards there won't make them grow.
303040.main: Did you rest well, Commander? Health comes first!|I'm not sure if Aoba is getting enough rest... Please make sure to check up on her!|Work hard, play hard! That's the secret to a happy life!
303040.feeling5: Aoba is always so impatient! But she's my big sis, and she's very important to me. Just like you, Commander. You're precious to me as well!
303040.upgrade: Being wasteful is no good, Commander.
303040.unlock: Pleased to meet you! I'm Kinugasa. Have you been eating and sleeping well,  Commander? Don't be like my big sis... Speaking of which, is she also here by any chance?
303040.feeling4: I don't really like lecturing people... but I've gotten used to lecturing my sister, and you don't seem to mind. Eh? You actually it? Then... I guess I'll keep it up...
303040.feeling1: It's not like I care what you do...
303040.propose: Jeez, Commander. Your sleeves and collar are messy as always, even for such an important occasion. I'll lecture you later~ let's carry on with the ceremony!
303040.drop_descrip: Second ship of the {namecode:55}-class heavy cruisers, {namecode:56}.
303040.profile: Good day, I'm Kinugasa! I was in the 6th Fleet with my sister Aoba before it was disbanded. We fought together in many battles, like Wake Island, the Coral Sea, and the Solomon Islands. I'm not as lucky as her though... Anyways, Commander, try not to overwork yourself! Rest is important too!
303040.touch2: Please take a seat, Commander. We're going to discuss fleet discipline.
303040.mission: Commander, work will only pile up if you keep putting it off!
303040.home: Commander, it's important to balance work and rest. Since you just got back, why not take a quick break?
303040.win_mvp: Everyone, don't let your guard down just because we won!
303040.expedition: Commander, since you didn't go yourself, you should at least welcome back the girls who worked hard on the commission!
couple_encourage: Stop looking around, sister!
303040.mail: Commander, do I have to tell you to check your mail every single time?
303040.feeling3: Don't be too hard on my sister... She actually has a lot of guilt buried in her heart.
303040.lose: We need to call a meeting and review this performance...

301054.detail: This outfit feels light and easy to move in, not bad at all... Very cute? Um... thank you...
301054.touch: Commander, this dress is made with really comfortable materials... Want to feel...?
301054.login: Commander, the girls from the Dragon Empery seem to be having a banquet... Want to come with me to have a look?
301054.main: This year's zodiac animal is... Eh? Commander, did you see where the piglet ran off to? |Commander, are we under attack? I hear a lot of explosions... Eh? So those are a form of celebration? That sounds interesting, yes... |What is this "ding-a-ling" sound? It reminds me... of our New Year back home...
301054.feeling5: I wish you a happy and peaceful holiday~ Commander, I hope that we can continue being together like this forever...
301054.unlock: Compared to the way we celebrate New Year in the Sakura Empire, the festivities of the Dragon Empery have a completely different atmosphere... But, I don't really mind the liveliness... Commander, do you like festivals?
301054.drop_descrip: Compared to the way we celebrate New Year in the Sakura Empire, the festivities of the Dragon Empery have a completely different atmosphere... But, I don't really mind the liveliness... Commander, do you like festivals?
301054.touch2: Commander, you can't... lift that part...

805012.detail: Believe, atone, and pray. Seek a new day... that you may grasp hold of your happiness, and the road to the light.
805012.touch: You'd like to sit by my side? Up we go... Good kitty... Alright, here you go, Commander.
805012.login: It looks like you went out to take a glimpse of the morning sun. I look forward to being in your company today, Commander.
805012.main: nil|nil|What these fortunes tell may be your fate. Even so, is it not mankind's strength to overcome fate?|Shh. Lower your voice. I'm trying to get this one to warm up to Jean Bart.|Béarn, is it already time? ...Yes, I made a promise earlier to visit the shrine with everyone else. How would you like to come with us?
805012.feeling5: Settle down. Let us pray together. If I listen to your prayers and you listen to mine, you will come to understand that we are heading toward the same goal. Let us walk toward the light. You and I, together...
805012.unlock: Commander, I wish you a Happy New Year. May you avail yourself of the period of repose that follows the culmination of the year's duties. I pray that you and everyone else may receive the blessing of the Heavens.
805012.drop_descrip: Commander, I wish you a Happy New Year. May you avail yourself of the period of repose that follows the culmination of the year's duties. I pray that you and everyone else may receive the blessing of the Heavens.
805012.touch2: Is this a greeting... for the New Year?
805012.home: Please calm down and ponder what we should do. I'll be waiting right over here.
805012.expedition: It seems the commissions team made it back safely. This counts as good fortune, doesn't it?
805012.mail: So this is what the Sakura Empire's New Year's greeting cards look like... How interesting. Hehehe.

201019.detail: Hmm? Does my post-retrofit appearance interest you *that* much? How hopeless you are! Fine, gaze upon me!
201019.touch: U-unannounced intimacy is forbidden, you hear?!
201019.login: Stop sleeping on the job already! Straighten your back, eyes ahead! Sort yourself out!
201019.battle: Heheh! Now with my retrofit, you'll see my true potential!
201019.main: Stop looking at me like I only got this far thanks to you!|I just *have* to look after everyone, don't I! Both the rookies and you, Commander!|I-in all fairness, the Commander does a pretty good job most of the time... Ahem! N-never mind that! You just misheard me!
201019.unlock: Selecting me for a retrofit proves that you are a Commander of culture! Heheh, you'd better prepare yourself! From now on, I'll make sure to "take care" of you even more thoroughly!
201019.drop_descrip: Selecting me for a retrofit proves that you are a Commander of culture! Heheh, you'd better prepare yourself! From now on, I'll make sure to "take care" of you even more thoroughly!
201019.touch2: Who would've thought I'd get to use my new weapon so soon... Oh, Commander? I hope you've said your prayers!

305019.detail: I actually got a lot of things that I want to try, such as be as lively as {namecode:79}... hmm, is that too much?
305019.touch: Milord, do you like the dignified {namecode:78} or the livelier {namecode:78}?
305019.login: Milord, welcome back~ The profits show that today good things will happen~
305019.main: Becoming more… lively? Hehe, that must be merrited by Milord. |I feel… that bad luck still exists, but being together with you, Milord, has washed away all my bad luck. |{namecode:79} always tells me to look for my own happiness, and I think I’ve finally found it~
305019.unlock: Milord! Thank you~ Not just for the retrofit, but for many many things. Hehe, it was the greatest of fortune for me and {namecode:79} to meet you.
305019.drop_descrip: Milord! Thank you~ Not just for the retrofit, but for many many things. Hehe, it was the greatest of fortune for me and {namecode:79} to meet you.
305019.mission: Milord, can I also join you on this new mission?
305019.home: Milord, please wait, I’ve made really delicious treats meant especially for you.
305019.lose: Oh... no, we can’t blame all failures on our curse.

805010.detail: Place your faith in me. Follow my lead. Offer up your prayers. Seek the Lord. Only then will the path of God be opened...
805010.touch: Please listen to our prayers closely, Commander.
805010.login: Bonjour, Commander. Please relax and drink this tea while I carry out my morning prayers.
805010.battle: All ships, prepare for combat! For liberty and glory! Aux armes, marchons!
805010.feeling2: The one you are talking to was once despisingly called many things: the calamity that brought on war, the fearsome Cardinal, and the maniac possessed by religious fervor. I ask of you: when you look at me, what do you see in me?
805010.headtouch: May Heaven confer upon you its blessings.
805010.mission_complete: The reward for those who work hard is Heaven's grace. Let us accept it gratefully.
805010.main: I believe that any obstacle can be overcome with fervent faith and untiring efforts.|Those round little creatures... If I recall correctly, Algérie told me they're called "Meowfficers."|Have I met the Royal Navy yet? Yes. I hope to deepen our bond, so I'm bringing some wine to the next tea party.|Please make use of my precious allies, the Iris Templar Knights, at your discretion. After all, one of their missions is to fight for peace.|The relationship between those from the Eagle Union and those from the Iris Libre is a bit... Well, I get the feeling that Jean Bart would get along with them just fine, though.
805010.feeling5: The feeling of distance between people is an interesting thing indeed. A superior officer and their subordinate. The leader of a fleet and the highest post of the organization. A warship and... Hehe. For the time being, let's let the others continue misunderstanding our relationship, okay?
805010.upgrade: At times, might is needed to guide others on the right path. I give you my thanks.
805010.unlock: I am Richelieu, Cardinal of Iris Libre. If you too will fight for freedom and faith, then I shall bring you victory, Commander.
805010.feeling4: You've come by again. Haven't you been getting too friendly with me? ...Just kidding. I'm truly grateful to have another person that I can chat casually with. I hope that you feel the same way, too.
805010.feeling1: Those who refuse to stop marching shall face the path of ruin... Make sure you keep that in mind.
805010.propose: As the one who guides Iris Libre, I cannot make an oath solely to you. However, I vow to protect and support you for as long as I live. This, I vow, on the holy name of Iris...
805010.profile: I am Richelieu, the lead ship of the Richelieu class. During my history as a ship, I lived through good times and bad times, and I also witnessed the rise and fall of my homeland... This time, I hope to protect all that is dear to me up until the end. Together with this fleet, I strive for liberty and peace...
805010.touch2: If nothing else, your audacity is commendable.
805010.mission: Missions may be called a kind of trial. If you take them on with the proper attitude, there is no need to worry.
805010.home: Mission complete. The fleet has safely returned to the port. Good work, Commander.
805010.win_mvp: May the wandering souls drifting about the battlefield find eternal peace and salvation... Amen...
805010.expedition: I'd like to report that the commissions have been safely completed, and that fleet operations are running smoothly. You've done a good job, Commander.
couple_encourage: As long as we have Heaven's divine protection, we have nothing to fear!
It seems that we fight together once again.
Please fight to your heart's content. I have your back.
Brethren! Assemble under the banner of righteousness!
Bring down judgment upon the nonbelievers.
805010.mail: Letters are blessings from other people.
805010.feeling3: Commander, please have a seat. What would you like to drink? ...There's no need to be on guard. Even someone like me lives an ordinary life when not on duty or performing religious rites. A person cannot live on faith alone. Sometimes, you just need a drink or two. Hehe.
805010.lose: Is this... also a trial from Heaven...?

202152.detail: Commander, I often perform in the main plaza. It'd be nice if you could come and listen.
202152.touch: Are you tired of working? Well, is there anything you'd like to listen to?
202152.main: The pigeons always seem to gather to the sound of music. Hehe, turns out that they're hungry. |Commander, are you interested in learning an instrument? I'd recommend the piano so that you can accompany me! |Commander, if you ever find yourself lost and confused in the dark, you can always seek out my music!
202152.feeling5: Commander, after everything is over, let's travel around the world, bringing blessings to the far corners of the world with our music. This is something only we can do.
202152.unlock: I've always believed that music is unique in its power to touch one's heart, so I decided to learn the violin. Commander, please enjoy my performance.
