202152.drop_descrip: I've always believed that music is unique in its power to touch one's heart, so I decided to learn the violin. Commander, please enjoy my performance.
202152.touch2: Jeez, Commander, this is going to get in the way of my performance...
202152.home: You must be weary, Commander. Allow me to soothe you with my music.

101176.detail: Benson was also there when Javelin asked me to become an idol... When I saw the glint in her eye, I knew things weren't going to end well...
101176.touch: Commander, Laffey seems to be getting better at singing, because I can stand still now...
101176.main: All these lessons and rehearsals... What a pain... Can I just put on a show where I sleep while standing up? |Even though Benson said that Laffey would do the entire Planet Bunny proud by becoming an idol, it honestly sounds like a pain in the bun. However, the outfit she made for me is really cute... so maybe I can put in some effort for her sake. |I'm done with today's lessons... they were unexpectedly fun. |...I think I got some fanmail? Mm, it makes me a little happy..
101176.unlock: "Laffey came from Planet Bunny..." Umm, I forgot that line Benson told me to say... In any case, everyone, please give me lots of support... Actually, just a little support is fine... Uhh, I have to do it again with more motivation?
101176.drop_descrip: "Laffey came from Planet Bunny..." Umm, I forgot that line Benson told me to say... In any case, everyone, please give me lots of support... Actually, just a little support is fine... Uhh, I have to do it again with more motivation?
101176.home: I feel like I'm supposed to be doing something right now... but I can't remember what. Commander, want to take a nap with me?
101176.lose: Nnh... Can't get motivated after all all...

101440.detail: I have an incredible power inside me that will burst forth to save everyone at that critical moment... Yeah! That would be badass!
101440.login: It's nice to see your smiling face, Commander! Heh heh!
101440.hp_warning: I won't be afraid! Now more than ever, they need me!
101440.feeling2: Whenever you're in trouble, just call my name! Then you can bet Cooper will be there to bail you out, Commander!
101440.mission_complete: Mission accomplished! We're definitely making a difference!
101440.main: Paperwork? How does that help in a fight?|Aaahhh~ I just lose it whenever I see a kitty cat. Commander, let's keep one in the office, a black one!|Hey... how long are we gonna stay in the office? I'm so bored...
101440.feeling5: Commander! From now on I'm staying here with you, whether you call for me or not. So you won't have to worry about a thing...! Huh? You think I'm the one who's gonna get in trouble? Nng, yeah, maybe... But that still means I gotta stay with you, Commander!
101440.upgrade: Getting stronger is how I help more people!
101440.unlock: Hey Commander, I'm Cooper! Let's join forces and fight for the future of the world! Booyah!
101440.feeling4: Sorry, Commander. I know you were looking for me, but I got held up with this black kitty cat. I hope you didn't worry about me... B-but, like, who could resist playing with a kitty cat...?
101440.feeling1: Even if Commander is my enemy, I won't go soft!
101440.propose: Commander, who knew I was so important to you... I'm so happy! As long as I'm with you, then tomorrow... and the next day, and the day after that, I know I'll be able to do anything!
101440.drop_descrip: Allen M. Sumner-class destroyer – Cooper, Hull Number DD-695.
101440.profile: I'm an Allen M. Sumner-class destroyer, Cooper! I fought alongside Allen M. Sumner and Moale at Ormoc Bay, but I guess I didn't try hard enough... Nnng, damn it! How was I supposed to pick out anything like those oxygen torpedoes!
101440.touch2: Commander, do you understand what you're doing here?
101440.mission: We won't be able to help anyone if you leave your missions unfinished!
101440.home: Commander, I took care of a whole bunch of things while you were gone! See these reports? I wrote them all wrong? What the...
101440.win_mvp: Phew... What a nice feeling. Feels like victory.
101440.expedition: Go greet the team coming back from commission? Easy peasy! Just watch me~
101440.mail: A new message? Could it be a distress signal...? My Danger Antenna is tingling!
101440.feeling3: Commander! Did I hear my name? Hah hah hah, just point me at the enemy and... You need me to deliver these documents? I'm not your errand girl!
101440.lose: One little setback won't get me down!

301056.detail: Even though we were supposed to use our codenames, Kaga just went and spilled the beans. It's a bit troublesome when nobody is going to use them...
301056.touch: Commander, want an apple? They're really good.
301056.login: Commander, want to join Ayanami in cover ops training? ...Hmm, actually, that seems futile.
301056.battle: I'll show you the power... of Ayanami and her friends!
301056.main: Those Cloak of Invisibility things that they have in the Royal Navy are really cool... they make me a bit jealous... |When I need help, I usually turn to Shouhou or Zed. As for Fubuki... she always hears me out on a variety of stuff. I'm very thankful. |This cloak that Yuubari developed for me... has a function that "always conceals its wearer's face." That's... probably good. |Commander's office is always protected, and it is absolutely safe. There's no need to worry.
301056.upgrade: This power... is for the sake of protecting my friends...!
301056.unlock: Ayanami here. Successfully infiltrated Commander's office. Oh... Commander saw me. Operation failed...
301056.drop_descrip: Ayanami here. Successfully infiltrated Commander's office. Oh... Commander saw me. Operation failed...
301056.win_mvp: The enemy's lookouts have been taken out succcessfully. Thank you, Commander.
301056.mail: The mail's been... Oh, the members of the maid team responsible for protecting you have already looked it over. It's fine to open it.
301056.lose: The concealment function that Yuubari added was not very useful...

103030.detail: My armor's gotten thicker, but it feels like I'm more exposed than before...
103030.touch: Um, I'm a... little ticklish right there...
103030.login: With proper training, I think we could make quite the team, Commander.
103030.battle: The battle horn has sounded! C'mon, let's go!
103030.feeling2: I'm not really the talkative type, but if you're still willing to be my friend, then maybe...
103030.mission_complete: Rewards have arrived. You should check them out.
103030.main: You'll start to calm down if you just sit and listen to the waves...|Houston, you're too loud! Pipe the hell down!|Hold on, I'm thinking about something...
103030.feeling5: ... Someone I love, huh? Well, there is someone, but I don't think I can say their name just like that... Hey, Commander, aren't you a lot like me? Hornet always tells me I'm not good at adapting to new things, and neither are you...
103030.upgrade: Thank you. I'll have you rewarded for this later.
103030.unlock: Hm? Oh hey, Commander. If you can accurately predict where I'm gonna show up, then maybe we're in sync with each other... If only Hornet and I could be like that... *Sigh*...
103030.feeling4: Smiling? I guess it's true that I rarely smile... I'm a pretty stubborn girl, and I don't have many friends... Hm... If you like girls who smile, then I'll try to do that every now and then...
103030.feeling1: I'm getting distracted here, so do you think you could be quiet for a bit?
103030.propose: You finally realized it, didn't you, you dense man... But to be fair, I never had the courage to put it into words either... A-anyway, from now on, let's work together as dense partners in love, shall we?
103030.drop_descrip: Northampton-class Heavy Cruiser – Northampton, Hull Number CA-26!
103030.profile: I'm Northampton, a Washington Treaty cruiser. I participated in the Doolittle Raid and the Battle of Midway, and I've earned 6 battle stars. I regret not being able to bring Hornet back home in one piece...
103030.mission: Looks like that mission hasn't been completed yet. Let me handle it!
103030.home: Nobody got left behind, right? Then the fleet's safely made it back.
103030.win_mvp: I never thought I'd be able to do something like this...
103030.expedition: Hey, you have a commission that's been completed.
103030.mail: Commander, I've left your mail on the desk.
103030.feeling3: I have a buddy who's a bit noisy and little sisters who are pretty rowdy, so having a friend like you who's rather quiet feels pretty unusual...
103030.lose: I knew we couldn't win that easily...

201020.detail: Is there something on my face?
201020.touch: Zzzzz... Ugh... I'm trying to sleep... don't poke me like that...
201020.battle: Everyone... calm down. Seize the chance and hit the enemy where it hurts.
201020.feeling2: I just can't be bothered... Maybe I should go to sleep...
201020.mission_complete: *Yawn*... Maybe the rewards are here now...
201020.main: Hmm? Not very talkative...? *Yawn*... I guess it's because I'm always so sleepy...|Wha...? Guess I fell asleep. With weather this fine, I couldn't help it...|You don't talk much, just like me, Commander. How nice...
201020.feeling5: I'm not all that talkative... but we don't even need words to understand each other... do we?
201020.upgrade: I've gotten stronger... I'll work harder, so look forward to that.
201020.feeling4: Commander... give this some thought: isn't it boring, being with me...?
201020.propose: ... Sorry... I'm just so happy that I don't even know what to say... I'll take good care of this...
201020.drop_descrip: A-class destroyer – Acasta, Hull Number H09.
201020.skill: Guess I should put in a little more effort...?
201020.profile: I'm Acasta... part of the A-class. Calling me "brave" would be flattery. I was just doing my job... I'm not all that strong, but I'll do my best if you need me to.
201020.touch2: Uhh... if anyone sees us, you'll get arrested.
201020.mission: Maybe you should take a look at the mission log?
201020.home: Welcome back... *Yawn*... Guess I'm a little sleepy...
201020.win_mvp: We won. Well, at least I didn't make a fool of myself, I guess.
201020.expedition: Zzzzzz... Hmm? Commander, shouldn't that commission be done by now?
201020.mail: Got some mail... Wonder if it's for you.
201020.feeling3: I know just the place to take a nap... You wanna come along and play hooky with me, Commander?
201020.lose: I figure this outcome isn't something to celebrate...

305021.detail: Milord, I heard that koi streamers can bring good fortune, so I brought some with me~
305021.touch: Ah, Milord! I’m trying to find the best spot to watch fireworks! Want to join me?
305021.login: Milord, Milord! Would you help me practice volleyball? It’d be too embarrassing if I let Cygnet beat me...
305021.main: Hawawa! The volleyball is coming my yay! When I stand next to {namecode:17}, I always seem to get hit by things...|Ugh... I still can’t light this fire. Stand back, Milord, I’m going to try using my cannons!|{namecode:78} tied this bell to my tail so I don’t have to worry about getting bitten by fish when I’m napping at sea... She’s so nice!
305021.unlock: It’s just not summer without beach volleyball! Ah... Milord, you’re not playing? But I went through all this effort to pick out a swimsuit...
305021.drop_descrip: It’s just not summer without beach volleyball! Ah... Milord, you’re not playing? But I went through all this effort to pick out a swimsuit...
305021.touch2: Woah...! Milord, next time, say "hi" to me first! I almost rammed my main gun right into you!
305021.home: Milord is back! Ugh... it’s so hot! The fan is even blowing hot air!

103162.detail: I'm radiating unusually dark vibes? Thanks for the compliment. I guess these decal tattoos Bremerton recommended are doing their job. As in, they make people a little more cautious around me than they normally would be.
103162.touch: I know I'm eyecatching, but I didn't hope you'd stare so intensely at me... I mean, that's not to say I *don't* want you stare at me, but...
103162.login: All right, let's do like always and breeze through these tasks.
103162.main: Bremerton's got a real knack for psychological warfare. She often gives me good advice on how to present myself.|I'm an expert at tennis, as you'd expect. If anything, you'd be kinda hard-pressed to find a sport I *don't* excel at.|So Commander, are you free after we're done here? Hahah, what, is it *that* unusual of me to ask if you wanna hang out?
103162.unlock: Heya, you here to watch the game? Heh, heavy cruiser Baltimore, the passerby solver of troubles, here to play it cool!
103162.drop_descrip: Heya, you here to watch the game? Heh, heavy cruiser Baltimore, the passerby solver of troubles, here to play it cool!
103162.touch2: Eep?! Come on, I've *told* you I'm sensitive to this sort of stuff!
103162.win_mvp: You don't need to know why I look this way. Because if you did, you'd vanish from this world. I'm just kidding around. Hahaha!

105140.touch: I'm ready to move out anytime.
105140.battle: Come at me with all you got!
105140.feeling2: Your will is my command, Commander.
105140.mission_complete: Commander, the mission rewards have arrived.
105140.main: In the darkness, my will was tempered. I fear nothing.|As long as I am of use to Commander, I am fine with handing my credit over to others.|Those who stand as Commander's enemies, are enemies all the same.
105140.feeling5: So this is your perspective, Commander... I choose how I live, was what you said... This time, I fight not for my duty, but for the sake of your smile, Commander.
105140.unlock: I am South Dakota, Commander. I shall become your shield and protect you from all cannon fire.
105140.feeling4: Another way to live other than fighting? I... do not know what to do, Commander. I have always lived like this... Can you teach me?
105140.propose: I feel warm when you're by my side, Commander. Your goals bring me the drive to fight. I become happy when I hear your words... I once offered you my shields. From now on... I give you my heart.
105140.drop_descrip: South Dakota-class battleship –  South Dakota, Hull Number BB-57!
105140.profile: Battleship of Eagle Union, South Dakota. When it comes to battlefields, I wish for you to not leave my side. I will protect you, Commander. 'The Strongest Shield'? Vain titles are worthless. There's meaning only in being useful.
105140.touch2: If this is what you want to do...
105140.mission: Commander, please do not forget about completing the missions.
105140.win_mvp: Partial victories aren't worth celebrating, Commander.
105140.expedition: The commission teams are back... If it is necessary, send me off as well.
couple_encourage: Don't just focus on firing. Keep surveying the area!
Sorry, I might have to bother you again.
Enterprise! Victory is now!
Kaede's Legion... Nice name!
105140.feeling3: I exist to help you achieve your goals, Commander. Other than that, I have no real value... A skirt? I've never worn something so fluffy before.
105140.lose: I am sorry, Commander... It's a shame...!

301057.detail: Z23 is always looking out for us... Even though she has her own schedule to worry about, she always helps us manage ours.
301057.touch: Commander, this is what I learned from my lessons today.
301057.login: Commander, I'm currently practicing my dance routine. Want to watch?
301057.battle: An idol's duty is to protect everyone's smiles!
301057.main: Singing and dancing are no problem for me, but smiling is hard... Javelin said that's what makes me cute though. Is that true, Commander? |Commander, Z23 told me that rock n' roll and idols don't really go together. Do you think I could make metal cute?|Fubuki seems to also be doing idol training. We should go see her... in a little bit. |I never knew that there were so many things to do as an idol. I'm getting all fired up.
301057.unlock: I guess I'm making my idol debut? Um, Javelin and the others are making their debuts, so, I also had to... Commander, what are idols supposed to do normally?
301057.drop_descrip: I guess I'm making my idol debut? Um, Javelin and the others are making their debuts, so, I also had to... Commander, what are idols supposed to do normally?
301057.home: If I imagine performances to be like battles, and think of the audience as enemies... Err, wait, that's not going to work.

201160.detail: Nothing can be achieved without repeated practice. Your Excellency, you should know this quite well, yes?
201160.touch: Eek?! ...Your Excellency? Please don't suddenly touch me like that!
201160.login: You seem to be running a little late. Your Excellent, please begin your work soon.
201160.battle: Look alive! Don't give the enemies an opening!
201160.hp_warning: I've got to hang in there...!
201160.feeling2: ...Ugh! Um, Your Excellency... My apologies, but when I feel an unfamiliar presence approach me... Ahem! In any case, it's my policy to not let my guard down.
201160.mission_complete: Look, Your Excellency! We've gotten so many rewards!
201160.main: There's something relaxing about this office, hmm... W-woah?! I, I'm not nodding off!|I may be a flotilla leader, but that's because I've earned the trust of my sister ships. It's not like I have a higher rank than them.|Hunter, I bet you ate my cake again! ...Oh, sorry, Your Excellency, did I disturb you?
201160.feeling5: Your Excellence, even if you try to sneak up on me, I've already memorized your aura... Eek?! Wh-why are you hugging me? Ahaha... It t-tickles, it tickles!
201160.upgrade: Phew... Though I've become stronger, I can't afford to lapse in my training...
201160.unlock: It's an honour to meet you, Your Excellency. Hardy, destroyer of the Royal Navy, reporting for duty.
201160.feeling4: Overthinking can have unintended consequences...? I see, I'll keep that in mind.
201160.propose: I know! I know you're going to tell me to not overthink things! But, I have to tell you as well... Your Excellency, you're too slovenly at times! I'll be watching your every move from now on, so prepare yourself!
201160.skill: I won't give you an opening!
201160.profile: I am Hardy, flotilla leader of the Royal Navy's H-class. At the Battle of Narvik, I led an assault on an Iron Blood port. We were able to land a heavy blow, but the enemy reinforcements... If only I had more time back then...
201160.touch2: This rapier may be decorative, but the business end still hurts!
201160.mission: Your Excellency, let's begin the mission after reviewing the documents.
201160.home: Your Excellency, is there anything we should reflect upon regarding this previous battle?
201160.win_mvp: Everyone, this victory is even more reason to not let your guard down.
201160.expedition: As a leader, if you have the right to give orders to others, then you must also cherish their contributions.
couple_encourage: This time, Lady Warspite, let us go together!
Glory unto you, Your Majesty!
201160.mail: Your Excellency, don't assume I'll be getting the mail for you every time!
201160.feeling3: A tea party...? Thank you for your consideration, but I still have to finish my training... B-but, I'd appreciate it if you could bring me a slice of cake...
201160.lose: Don't stay here! Please withdraw immediately!

305020.login: Milord, milord! What shall we do today?
305020.battle: Everyone, go~! Waaah?! My guns fired on accident!
305020.feeling2: Milord, come play with me! Ah... I forgot to bring stuff to play with... what should we do?
305020.mission_complete: Milord, milord! I've brought the rewards... Oops!
305020.main: Milord, Milord! Waah~! ...Thank you, milord. I have always tipped over easily, but I am used to it now.|Milord, do you want to jog with me? I want to become a little faster.|The vase in the hallway broke... It wasn't me, I swear! It just jumped off right as I walked past it...
305020.feeling5: I know how hard my big sister works, so for her sake, I know that I should allow myself to be happy. That way, I can share my happiness with her. Now that you are here, Milord, I think I'll finally be able to do that. I feel so happy every time I see you!
305020.unlock: Woah! It's Milord! Milord in person! Um... I'm Yamahi-, {namecode:79}! I am pleased to make your acquaintance.
305020.feeling4: Your Majesty, do you know this mask? It's a fox mask used in Kagura. Hehe, I'm actually about to practice my Kagura dance now. Do you want to watch?
305020.feeling1: You're so boring, Milord. I don't want to play with you anymore.
305020.propose: Milord? You're going to give this to me? ...Even though I am slow-footed and far from perfect? Milord, you are far too kind. I love you too.
305020.profile: Um... I'm big sister {namecode:78}'s little sister, {namecode:79}! Neither of us have really had good fortune since we were born, but I've grown up well thanks to big sis! Please don't judge me by my looks... I was once the flagship of the Combined Fleet! Planes...? What are those? Can I eat them?
305020.touch2: Woah! Watch out, Milord! I'm about to fire my main gun!
305020.home: Welcome back, Milord, I made you some tea... Woah! Watch out!
305020.win_mvp: Milord, did you see that? Did you?
305020.expedition: Milord, the girls have returned from commissions!
305020.mail: Milord! Milord! Your mail is here!
305020.feeling3: I love my sister, but she's a bit too quiet sometimes. Milord, I like spending time with you more because you'll play with me!

301050.detail: I've inspected the communication equipment. It won't cause any more problems...
301050.login: Commander, have you eaten yet? Here's some snacks.
301050.hp_warning: I don't want... to be alone...
301050.feeling2: Ayanami's impressions of Commander? I don't really know.
301050.headtouch: I don't really get it but... I'm a bit happy...
301050.mission_complete: The rewards for the previous mission are here.
301050.main: {namecode:6}'s ears... are they cute? I don't understand... As long as you're happy, Commander!|I've been having nightmares of all the girls getting lost... I'm certain that it's my fault, too...|Commander? No, nothing. I just wanted to see if you were here or not.
301050.feeling5: I don't particularly... like or dislike combat. I just do what must be done. But if it's for you, Commander... maybe I can get a bit stronger.
301050.unlock: I'm... Ayanami. I am often called the "Demon." Pleasure to meet you.
301050.feeling4: If there's one thing that worries me... it would be when you are not at my side.
301050.feeling1: I don't really want to get any closer.
301050.propose: Rest assured... This time, no matter what happens, I'll survive and return to you... because I'll always want to see you again...
301050.drop_descrip: First ship of special Type II {namecode:6} class destroyers, {namecode:6}.
301050.skill: Bear witness to the true power of the "Demon"
301050.profile: I am Ayanami, an improved Fubuki-class destroyer. I am not afraid of combat. Though just a destroyer, I can fight any enemy...
301050.touch2: Commander... please... don't touch there so much... It's making me feel weird...
301050.mission: Commander, we've been notified of new missions.
301050.home: Commander, you're a little like me on the battlefield... That's... pretty cool.
301050.win_mvp: MVP? I don't really get it, but... thanks.
301050.feeling3: Commander, you're always saying that my ears are cute... But why won't you touch them?

402010.detail: Remember, it’s unwise to place too much faith into the numbers.
402010.touch: Oh? You seem fairly energetic today. Let's do some more training.
402010.login: Now then, let us begin today’s training.
402010.battle: It's time to see what we learned from our training... and make our enemies tremble before us!
402010.feeling2: Hey! What were you trying to do? Don't be shy... just tell me.
402010.mission_complete: Oh? Mission complete? Well done, Commander. Don't forget to collect your rewards!
402010.main: Making an expression like that... are you after some of big sister’s rough affection?|You should never ask about a woman’s age, Commander.|Whipping doesn’t actually hurt that much once you’re used to it. Want to give it a go?
402010.feeling5: To train someone, the trainer must also give the trainee some love, otherwise... Yes, Commander, I love you. Come, let's continue. What should we try next?
402010.upgrade: I think I get the hang of it! Commander, come with me for a second!
402010.unlock: So you’re the commander? You have such a cute face! Hehe... let big sister take "good care" of you from now on~
402010.feeling4: Hmm? I do you like you very much, in many different ways... I'm going to teach you all kinds of things from now on... Hehe...
402010.feeling1: Alright, time for me to punish you.
402010.propose: Commander, you’re the best! The best what? Pet? Companion? Or maybe... lover~?
402010.skill: Hmm, do you want some lessons from me too?
402010.profile:
I'm the first ship of the Königsberg-class light cruisers, Königsberg. I began serving in the Iron Blood Navy a long time ago.
I've participated in far more training and transporting missions than actual combat, so feel free to refer to me as your teacher. Understood?
402010.touch2: Oh my? That’s not how you do it. Should I teach you the proper way to touch a girl?
402010.mission: Let's see what mission is up next.
402010.home: Good work, Commander. Let’s quickly review the previous battle.
402010.win_mvp: Hmph, so that’s all they amounted to.
402010.expedition: The girls have returned from commissions. Please welcome them back in a timely manner.
402010.mail: Remember to read new mail as soon as possible. It’s rude to make people wait.
402010.feeling3: And I thought you were a good child, Commander... I guess you can still be trained... Hehe...
402010.lose: Tsk... Do we still not have enough anti-air?

102100.detail: You wanna get to know me? Sure thing. Inspect me to your heart's content.
102100.touch: Gee, thanks! You made my bubble pop!
102100.login: Another day of calm weather! Nice!
102100.battle: Dang, guess I've got no choice! I'll show you the might of us Southerners!
102100.feeling2: Commander, it's sunny outside, so why don't we go for a walk? It's unhealthy to stay indoors all the time!
102100.mission_complete: Today's missions were a breeze! Total walk in the park!
102100.main: What tunes do I listen to? Good question. See if you can guess! ... Rock 'n' roll? Bzzzt, wrong!|Bleh, my sis snatched my sunglasses again...|Once this war is over, maybe I should give Eagle Union football a try...
102100.feeling5: When I can't see you on my days off, I feel kinda lonely... Geez, look at you, making a girl say stuff like this! A-aren't you ashamed of yourself?! Jerk!
102100.unlock: Cleveland-class light cruiser number 2, Columbia! That's me~! Not the Columbia in D.C., the one in South Carolina! Geez, listen to me! Not the Columbia with Bogotá as its capital!
102100.feeling4: Why do I wear only one sock? That's a secret! If you're so curious, try taking it off~ Hehehe♪
102100.feeling1: *Sigh*... So that's all, huh. I was wrong to get my hopes up.
102100.propose: Yeah... thanks. Even when we're not on the battlefield, we'll always be together... No, wait, cheesy lines like this are totally out of character for me! Anyhow, right now, I feel so happy!
102100.drop_descrip: Cleveland-class light cruiser – Columbia, hull number CL-56.
102100.skill: Don't blame me if you get hit!
102100.profile: Hiii! It's me, the girl who scooted through the Pacific and earned 10 battle stars: Columbia! Hey, now, no need to sing my praises, go see Cleveland and sing hers instead! Need anything else? Alright, then I'll get back to patrolling.
102100.touch2: Commander, is it this star on my shirt you like? Or is it... what's underneath it~?
102100.mission: I only just started chewing this gum, and we've already got a new mission...?
102100.home: You're back~! I've been chewing on this gum so long it's lost all its taste.
102100.win_mvp: That was nothing special~ I do it all the time~
102100.expedition: The commission team's back! Aren't you gonna go thank them?
couple_encourage: Hey, sis~ You really do need my support, don't you?
102100.mail: Aren't you gonna check your mail? There might be something nice in there.
102100.feeling3: Hm? You'd never have guessed that I'd be into ballet? ... What's that supposed to mean?! Laugh one more time and I'll punch you!

401360.detail: Hmhmm~ what do you think about my bewitching heterochromatic eyes? H-hey! They're not contacts!
401360.touch: W-wait! Even if it's you, Commander, I won't let you unwrap- I mean, unseal my powers! No way! Nuu~!
401360.login: Ohh, you came at just the right time! Hm, want to listen to my brand new song? It's called "Devilish Overture!"
401360.battle: Seal... released! Come! I'll burn the power of a Devilish Idol into your retina! Shazam!
401360.feeling2: Heheh~ Finally, someone able to see on the same wavelength as the Devilish Idol herself! Now, become my fan!
401360.headtouch: Bear witness to my devilish procession! Wh-what... Commander, I won't grow any taller if you keep patting me like that!
401360.mission_complete: The stars have rewarded our efforts. Blink and you'll miss the opportunity, Commander!
401360.main: Commander, have you seen Fünf? I granted her some of my devilish powers, but then suddenly lost the ability to detect her with my bewitching eyes... Huh? Oh, she's right there? |Nobody can resist the bewitching songs of the Devilish Idol! |Whether it's on the battlefield or on the stage, once I release my sealed powers, nothing can get in my way~!
401360.feeling5: Gah... Commander, when I'm with you, I can feel endless power welling up from deep within me, even without releasing my seal. Perhaps this is the "love" I have for you, ehehe~♪
401360.upgrade: My devilish powers of bewitchment... have further awakened within me!
401360.unlock: Hm hm~ so you're my Commander? Our meeting must have been ordained by the Fates. By the Iron Blood coursing through my veins, the Devilish Idol Z36 binds herself to your service! Shazam!
401360.feeling4: Those who share the seal of the Devilish Idol shall have their fate cosmically bound with mine! That means... I kind of like you! Ehehe~
401360.feeling1: My bewitching eyes have foreseen your imminent destruction!
401360.propose: I can feel it... my devilish soul resonating with yours, Commander...! Okay, I've decided! Until the end of time, whether on the battlefield or on the stage, I shall remain by your side, and use my devilish powers for you only! Commander, you'll always stay with me, right?
401360.skill: I'll engrave my devilish powers of bewitchment upon your body!
401360.profile: I am the Bremen-born destroyer Z36, known by many as the Devilish Idol! My friends and I travelled throughout the Baltic Sea, but eventually I was dragged into that deep, black abyss... Hmph. In any case, I'll bring you victory with my powers of bewitchment!
401360.touch2: You'll get hexed for casually touching the Devilish Idol's body!
401360.mission: Aldebaran has illuminated our path forward! Everyone, the time to act is now!
401360.home: Phew... Huff... Why am I so worn out? Heh, that's because I've been practicing my powers of bewitchment! Ahhh, fine, fine! I was practicing for my performance...
401360.win_mvp: This victory was ordained by the Fates! Yes, that means it was inevitable!
401360.expedition: My long-departed kindred have finally returned to us from their commission. Let us greet them with hearts full of gratitude!
couple_encourage: Let's have our devilish duet! Huh?! Fünf, come baaack!
401360.mail: A letter from one of my worshippers? Hmph... it's addressed to you, Commander.
401360.feeling3: Heheh~ allow me to engrave the seal of the Devilish Idol upon your flesh! W-wait, I'm not done making the stamp yet!
401360.lose: Ugh... a Devilish Idol never loses...!

301051.touch: I think... I like this costume.
301051.main: Are these... sweets? Thank you. I will try them.|There are fun things outside of combat and training too...|If I stand on this pumpkin lantern... will I be closer to reaching the skies?
301051.unlock: I heard that... I need to wear a costume like this to participate in Halloween festivities. Commander... do I look cute?
301051.drop_descrip: I heard that... I need to wear a costume like this to participate in Halloween festivities. Commander... do I look cute?
301051.touch2: Tonight, I am not a demon... but a witch!

301300.detail: Hoho~ What about me's gotten you so interested?
301300.login: Aha, you've finally showed up~! Will we be doin' anything interesting today?
301300.battle: Watch out for them submarines and torpedoes. Full speed ahead!
301300.feeling2: Commander, only rookies and small-timers judge equipment by how new it is.
301300.mission_complete: Hm? Payment for those duties? Right then, take care bringing 'em here!
301300.main: Winners are those who hold out 'till the very end!|Hawksbill! That girl couldn't beat me, but she put up a real good fight.|Those Fifth Carrier Division folks... they're pretty nice...
301300.feeling5: Commander... Ya know, I like you~ Oh dear, your face is all red~ So red it's even reached your ears~!
301300.upgrade: Yup, I'm just oozing with energy~ Hoho~! Now I can go on another rampage~
301300.unlock: {namecode:124}, First Destroyer Division ship number one, has arrived. Are you certain you're the commander? Then things are gonna get interesting from now on. *Giggle* Enjoy watching me do my work~
301300.feeling4: Well, Commander, what type of girl do you fancy~? Me? Maybe someone more refined? ... But is that really true? Right, I've got that on tape now~! Now the question is: who will I play it to~?
301300.feeling1: You're more boring than I ever imagined, Commander.
301300.propose: Commander, it ain't too late to change your mind yet~ Yeah, that's it, take your time thinking about me~ Hm? The door? Oh no, it looks like it's been locked shut~ What will we do~?
301300.skill: Sorry, ain't got time for one-on-ones.
301300.profile: I'm {namecode:124}, {namecode:124}-class destroyer number one. I was a part of the First Destroyer Division. My name's got a mighty ring to it, don'tcha think? Hoho~! I fought in numerous battles in the Pacific Islands since the start of the World War, so me being a fleet veteran ain't just for show or me being whimsical. I may not look it, but ASW is my forte. Every time I think about my battle with that wolf pack my blood starts to boil~
301300.touch2: Well well, looks like your naughty desires are starting to show themselves. How about an exorcism for ya?
301300.mission: Duties, eh. How's about we go give it a look?
301300.home: Look at you, back safe and sound! Reward yourself with a sip of my nutritious drink! Hey now, don't be shy~!
301300.win_mvp: You see this? This is what years of experience looks like!
301300.expedition: Guess the commission team's back again all in one piece. Hum hum, splendid!
couple_encourage: It's time for us to stand together again!
301300.mail: Mail, eh... It ain't an errand from the Union, is it...?
301300.feeling3: My hobbies? 3 rounds of food and sleep and a bit of teasin' you. Hohoho~! That look there is what I wanted to see.
301300.lose: Ugh... Should've known I can't keep up like this...

305030.detail: Commander, allow me to show you what real bullet hell looks like!
305030.touch: What? W-What do you mean an aviation battleship can't fly? Lame!
305030.login: Let's go have a swell time on the seas, Commander!
305030.battle: Finally! My turn to make some noise.
305030.feeling2: It'd be wonderful to be able to go stargazing with {namecode:77} again.
305030.mission_complete: Mmhmmm~! All I need is a beer and a raw egg to wake up. Do you want some too?
305030.main: We're fine without fuel. All you need out on the seas is some good food and booze!|What should I call {namecode:78}? Big sister? Senpai?|Ise Shrine? I've seen it from a distance, but they won't let me go in...
305030.feeling5: I could have any number of friends stronger than me, but you Commander... Ahaha! You're an idiot, I'm an idiot! Cheers~!
305030.upgrade: A flight deck, eh? I wish I could fly...
305030.unlock: I'm the Sakura Empire battleship who fired the last full volley during the war: Ise-Class battleship, Ise!
305030.feeling4: Commander, I brought some snacks. Why don't we have some drinks tonight?
305030.propose: Thank you~! I'm going to stay by your side until the end of the end. Why? Because I hate drinking alone!
305030.profile: {namecode:76}, first ship of the {namecode:76}-class battleships! I was on perimeter guard when Pearl Harbor was attacked. I was then recalled and remodeled as an aviation battleship. Then I was recalled again... Tsk! Some ships have a long list of battles, but no one was patient enough to wait for me to join in! We're super dreadnought ships... You would think they'd want our help! *Sigh* Anyways, it's great to finally catch up with the main fleet!
305030.touch2: Commander, you really want to know what it feels like to fly, don't you? Please feel free to climb into my cannon.
305030.mission: I... I'm coming too! Wait for me!
305030.home: Tsk... I haven't had a chance to play- Ahem... Commander, I've been guarding our rear just as you asked!
305030.win_mvp: Ahaha! As a super dreadnought, it's only natural!
305030.expedition: Operation Kita was more fun that this!
305030.mail: Whoo! Just the thing to prop up the corner of the table!
305030.feeling3: Compared to that time, life is a lot more vivid and entertaining now. Cheers, Commander!

307011.detail: Akagi picked this swimsuit out just for you, Commander~! Are you falling in love with me even more deeply?
307011.touch: Commander, what were you doing with that "Rodney" girl?
307011.login: Ahh... Welcome back, my dear Commander. I wonder where you've been. Take your clothes off so I may know if the smell of vixens lingers on you~
307011.main: Commander, it's dangerous to be separated at sea. Please hold my hand tightly~|Relax, Kaga. You're my only friend. You'll always have a place by my side.|Wait until tonight, Commander. Kaga and I shall use our planes to hold a most spectacular fireworks show for you!
307011.unlock: "When you gaze long into the abyss, the abyss also gazes into you." Commander, please do not forget that when you gaze at Akagi~ *giggles*
307011.drop_descrip: "When you gaze long into the abyss, the abyss also gazes into you". Commander, please do not forget that when you gaze at Akagi~ *giggles*
307011.touch2: Commander, won't you come teach me how to swim? Oh? What did you just say~?
307011.expedition: Has the commission fleet returned? If you're going, won't you take Akagi with you?

103163.detail: Bremerton said, "When you change your look, your mannerisms usually change too" and suggested this dress to me... She must be snickering at me actually wearing it right now...
103163.touch: Woah?! Ah, thanks... Guess it's a real uphill battle, getting used to these high heels...
103163.login: Oh, you can sit here if you want to, Commander. I'll just... stand here for a while and accustom myself to this look.
103163.main: I should've gone with a less cumbersome outfit, shouldn't I? Maybe something like Cleveland's suit... Yeah, that would've worked...|I'll bet tons of girls want to share a drink with you tonight, right, Commander? Go on, chat with them before I get you wasted. Or you can just stay here, hahahah.|The mirror? It's so I can see my– Oh god!
103163.unlock: Damn, that Bremerton... What did she make me wear this time... Even though I was the one to ask her for advice... Um... Ugh... This doesn't look too weird, right...?
103163.drop_descrip: Damn, that Bremerton... What did she make me wear this time... Even though I was the one to ask her for advice... Um... Ugh... This doesn't look too weird, right...?
103163.home: "H-Hiii! You want to dance with me?" ...Oh god, no, that's way too forced. I need to sound natural for– Eep! W-when'd you get here, Commander?!

407011.detail: Now that I think about it, other than forcing me to wear this skimpy bit of fabric, what else is this summer season even for?
407011.touch: Is it time to depart? Wait a moment, these shoes are a bit hard to put on... Come help me out for a second...
407011.login: Didn't we agree to go to the beach? Where were you?
407011.main: Is there a nice vantage point on the beach to sit at? ...There isn't? Oh well... |I only wore this... "clothing" because you told me to. If you didn't come to the beach with me, I'd be... rather upset. |Eugen, don't rush me, the commander is still working. What am I going to do on the beach by myself...
407011.unlock: So the Second Movement is a Lento of the summer and the sea? So be it... Since we will arrive at the Finale eventually, I suppose I can enjoy this moment of fleeting peace with you.
407011.drop_descrip: So the Second Movement is a Lento of the summer and the sea? So be it... Since we will arrive at the Finale eventually, I suppose I can enjoy this moment of fleeting peace with you.
407011.touch2: Hmph... Commander, do you also wish to become food for this child here?

105141.detail: Aurora asked me to perform with her... I guess it can't hurt to try.
105141.login: What song should I play for you today...
105141.main: I can't get used to this flimsy dress. I'd rather wear my regular clothes...|My cat goes for the keyboard when I'm not playing... Do you want to practice the piano too, kitty?|We can express so much through music. I suppose that's fitting for someone bad at expressing their feelings like I am.
105141.feeling5: Without you, I doubt I would've ever come to understand what splendor this world holds, or started playing the piano either... Commander, I'd like to play you a song that's important to me.
105141.unlock: Massachusetts suggested I learn something useful that's unrelated to combat, so I started playing the piano... It seemed impossible at first, but after actually trying it, I've developed a pretty good feel for it.
105141.drop_descrip: Massachusetts suggested I learn something useful that's unrelated to combat, so I started playing the piano... It seemed impossible at first, but after actually trying it, I've developed a pretty good feel for it.
105141.mission: Music and instruments are simply hobbies. We ought to prioritize our missions, Commander.
105141.home: Everyone's back safe and sound. Now I can resume practicing with peace of mind.

307010.detail: Commander, are you keeping {namecode:91} in your most secret of thoughts? Mmm, how delightful~.
307010.login: Ah, welcome back... Commander, if you had taken any more of your sweet time, I would have turned this place into a sea of fire~
307010.battle: Are you girls also trying to get close to Commander? Ahahaha!
307010.feeling2: We were destined to meet. I knew at first sight that you were the one I’ve been looking for my whole life.
307010.mission_complete: Rewards? Being together with you, Commander, is all the reward I need.
307010.main: Commander, you’re so cute when you are hard at work. Just watching you makes me feel like I’ll overheat~|Don’t make fun of me for being slow-footed. See? I’ve~ caught~ you~|You smell like... that girl! Commander, Akagi needs to step out for a bit~
307010.feeling5: Commander... With this, nothing will get between us ever again... Your embrace, your smile, your scent... all belong to me.
307010.upgrade: Commander, your love is filling up {namecode:91}'s chest...
307010.unlock: We finally meet, Commander. However, there appear be too many eyesores here. Please allow me to "clean up" a bit before we deepen our relationship. Hehehe~
307010.feeling4: Commander, why were you talking to that girl? Weren’t you coming to see {namecode:91}? She was tempting you? Then... {namecode:91} is going to make her disappear.
307010.feeling1: If Commander was cut up into little pieces, he would never be able to leave Akagi’s side or break her heart ever again... Ahahaha!
307010.propose: I have waited an eternity for this day to come. No one shall be able to separate us ever again! My mind, body, and soul belong to you, as yours all belong to me. Haha... ahahahaha!
307010.skill: My love is invincible! Ahaha... ahahaha!
307010.profile: I am the glorious Akagi, the pride of the peerless First Carrier Division. With my famed air wing, I shall overcome any battle as long as you are with me. Yes, Commander, as long as we are together...
307010.touch2: If you so desire, I would not mind if you partake of me in front of all the others.
307010.mission: A new mission... is another opportunity to deepen our bonds. *giggles*
307010.home: Five Minutes of Fate? You mean every five minutes that we spend together?
307010.win_mvp: I will do anything for Commander’s sake, even if I must slay a god.
307010.expedition: I was hoping that they wouldn’t have come back at all... Commander, I’ve already confirmed the completion of the commission. No more than a glance should be needed from you.
couple_encourage: Am I beautiful, Commander?
Look out for friendly fire~!
I'm very tolerant, you know...
Commander, are you testing {namecode:91}'s love~?
307010.mail: Commander, who sent you this letter? A girl? Who is she?
307010.feeling3: You belong to me, and me only, Commander! That's something you should never forget, even if you are in charge of an entire fleet... Or else...
307010.lose: This wound is nothing compared to the thought of you abandoning me, Commander!

108050.detail: My new gig must leave me with little time to play pranks? Haha, my friend, a true idol can perform AND play pranks, too! If you want an example, look no further than Sara!
108050.touch: I wouldn't be here without your support!
108050.login: Morning there, P! Let's make the most of today!
108050.feeling2: Being an idol's pretty good! I get to sing, dance, and smile for a massive audience! ...That sounds nothing like what I'd enjoy? Really, huh?
108050.main: Surprise! How's my new stage prop look?|Most of the stuff we're wearing was brilliantly handmade by Dido! Curious about that doll she's got, though. What's it represent?|I wanna see Taihou's concern in person! We should totally set some time aside for that!
108050.feeling5: I want to be your center-stage idol that dazzles the audience, Commander! Heh, just kidding! Our WHOLE unit has to reach stardom together, after all. Hehehe~
108050.upgrade: My idol rank has gone up!
108050.unlock: Lights! Camera! Albacore! Ahaha, don't worry about it, I'm just getting fired up over here! Oh, did you come up with a better idea? Tell me, tell me~
108050.feeling4: Oh, Commander! Morniiing! Did you see the note I left about a date? It's your job as the producer to see to our personal needs, y'know~ I'll write down whoever else wants one, so be sure to give it a look~
108050.feeling1: You're really ruining it for the other members, you know that?
108050.propose: Say what? Idols aren't allowed to be in relationships? Yeah, well, I was a shipgirl before I became an idol, so it's all fine! This pretty little ring is mine now~ As are you, Commander~
108050.drop_descrip: Lights! Camera! Albacore! Ahaha, don't worry about it, I'm just getting fired up over here! Oh, did you come up with a better idea? Tell me, tell me~
108050.profile: Here comes Albacore, submarine-slash-idol! I'm unique, I'm in the groove, so make some noise as I perform for you! Vocals, dancing, you name it, I can do it!
108050.touch2: I wonder what'd happen to you if I were to scream "I'm being molested!" right now... Wanna find out? Heheheh~
108050.home: Your next line is, "Why is Albacore prompting me to speak?"
108050.win_mvp: Encore! Encore until our next encounter!
108050.expedition: Teehee! I get this feeling like the commission team is about to enjoy a surprise concert!
couple_encourage: Yo, Taihou! How about a duo performance?
108050.mail: Uh, Tashkent, where's the Commander's mail? ...Oh, hi, Commander! No, just talking to myself!
108050.feeling3: Hey, is that for me, Commander? Aww, how nice of you~ In return, I'll keep quiet about how you were ogling us while we practiced~
108050.lose: Welp... I've got one final ace up my sleeve!

301310.detail: I wonder how my sisters are doing... I'm worried about them...
301310.touch: Yeah? Are you feeling tired? Then wait just a moment, I've finished making some snacks!
301310.login: You can't fight on an empty stomach, Commander! I made lots and lots of food, so eat to your heart's content!
301310.battle: Don't do anything too dangerous, okay?
301310.feeling2: If you don't have anything to do, you should tidy things up. Organization is fundamental to leading a good life.
301310.mission_complete: You've done great, Commander. Bravo, bravo!
301310.main: This thing I've got? It's what's known as a ladle. Yeah, if it was a little smaller you could even serve tea with it.|This place is lacking in greenery... We should put some potted plants in here, Commander~!|Ahhh, the smell of laundry hung out to dry in the sun~ Isn't it great?
301310.feeling5: You just need to focus on your goals and I'll handle all the minor details. I'm happy to help you with anything, not just combat or missions~!
301310.upgrade: Thanks! You could have saved caring about me for later, though.
301310.unlock: This is the fleet everyone's in, right? Seems pretty rowdy~ I'm Matsukaze! Nice meeting you!
301310.feeling4: Lately when I'm alone, I've been asking myself "is the commander taking care of himself?," "is he eating enough?," "does he think about me?"... Ahh, never mind that last one!
301310.feeling1: Sigh... Where did I go wrong with you...
301310.propose: You're saying you want to take a lifelong vow with me? Eheheh, sure~ Then I, Matsukaze, swear to always, always look after you!
301310.skill: Don't you dare try to hurt my commander!
301310.profile: I'm the Kamikaze-class destroyer Matsukaze! I was in Destroyer Division 5 along with my sisters. We're a little outdated compared to something like the Mutsuki-class, but we won't let any newer classes beat us when it comes to combat or escorts! ...Sigh... I wonder how Asakaze's team will fare without me...
301310.touch2: Eek?! ...Commander, sit right over there! You need to be scolded!
301310.mission: Are you doing your duty properly, Commander? I'm here if you need me.
301310.home: You must be tired after that last battle... Don't overexert yourself, come here and lie down.
301310.win_mvp: Heheh, you'll have a really bad time if you underestimate a veteran!
301310.expedition: The commission team is back, Commander. It's not nice to keep them waiting!
301310.mail: Letter for you, Commander! Want me to read it out loud?
301310.feeling3: Yeah... I'm pretty bad with electronics... You should teach me how to properly use them, Commander!
301310.lose: Ugh... I'll be fine, just make a break for it, everyone...

307013.detail: Commander, I knew you'd be busy at the party, so I waited until the very end for you. Now, your full and undivided attention shall belong to Akagi alone~ Hehe~♡
307013.touch: Commander, there's a vacant seat right next to me~ Wouldn't you like to come a bit closer~?
307013.login: Have you awoken, Commander? Akagi will always be at your side~
307013.main: I will not do anything that would tarnish your reputation, but... if any meddlesome pests insisted on getting in your way... Ehehe...|Indeed. While you were socializing, I made sure to strengthen our bonds with the other factions. At events like these, Shinano is horribly out of place, and if I may say so, the burden may be a bit too great for Nagato.|Commander, why won't you get drunk with me already... Haah, even though Akagi has been so lonely for so long...
307013.unlock: Commander, I've been waiting for you~ What a sinful one you are, to tempt Akagi like this for so long... But at long last, nobody will ever get between us again...♡
307013.drop_descrip: Commander, I've been waiting for you~ What a sinful one you are, to tempt Akagi like this for so long... But at long last, nobody will ever get between us again...♡
307013.touch2: It's just the two of us here... Yes, Commander, feel free to do whatever your heart so desires~
307013.home: A toast to your victorious return, Commander... Hehehe~
307013.win_mvp: My love shall burn everything away~ Ahahahaha!!
307013.expedition: Who will you send to greet the commission fleet?
307013.mail: A letter, huh? ...Hey, Commander? Just what kind of uncouth person would go out of their way to get between us at a time like this...?
307013.lose: At least... protect my friends and compatriots...!

201023.detail: Looking after rabbits is a lot more enjoyable than running around doing errands... There might be something therapeutic about looking after these cuties...
201023.touch: Zzz... Hnn... Oh! It seemed like I was taking a nap with the rabbits, huh...
201023.login: Commander, the tea's not ready yet... Hm, you're just here to watch me? Hrmm...
201023.main: If you don't get out of that teacup, I won't be able to pour the tea...|As soon as I touch these cute little bunny ears... Haau, it's cuteness overload...|Ardent, stop! You can't feed our snacks to the bunnies...
201023.unlock: Come on, stop running around and behave already... Ah, Commander? Umm, I'm currently looking after these rabbits... Hm, you're thirsty? Um, give me a moment and I'll whip something up for you...
201023.drop_descrip: Come on, stop running around and behave already... Ah, Commander? Umm, I'm currently looking after these rabbits... Hm, you're thirsty? Um, give me a moment and I'll whip something up for you...
201023.home: Glorious was shooting strange glances at me just earlier...

403070.detail: ...My guitar sounds a bit off today... Huh, try tuning it? Nah, that's not it, I just have to warm up a bit more...
403070.touch: Haah? Who gave you permission to touch me?!
403070.login: Lessons are finally done for the day. Good grief, why'd I ever agree to do this...!
403070.battle: I'm gonna show you what I'm made of!
403070.feeling2: I'm just laying this out there - if we're going to do it, then we're going to do it properly! I don't want a half-baked job... Hey, pay attention!
403070.mission_complete: Rewards, huh... It'd be better if Eugen wasn't constantly trying to get on my nerves...
403070.main: Hey idiot, tell me what's next on my schedule! How long do you intend to keep me waiting? |Deutschland, it's fine to be proud of your sister, but have some self-control! ...Jeez, you're so lucky to have such a reliable sister... Meanwhile, look what I'm stuck with... |Huh? Who asked you to be my publicist? I'll earn my own fans!
403070.feeling5: So, what's next on the agenda? You should already know, right? ...If you know, then hurry up and spit it out! Screw you! Stop teasing me already...!
403070.upgrade: Eugen, just you wait! I'll show you what I'm capable of!
403070.unlock: Huh? Why are you staring at me like I'm some weirdo? I'll have you know, it's not like I wanted to do this or anything!
403070.feeling4: Ahh, ahh... I'm doing pretty good today... H-huh?! Who gave you permission to watch me?! I just happened to have some free time, that's all! Go away and take care of your own work!
403070.feeling1: Huh? There's no way I'd be able to work with an imbecile like you!
403070.propose: H-huh?! Who would want a ring like this... Guh...! F-fine, you can p-put it on... Happy now? Let's wrap this up already. The stage we're aiming to be on is much loftier than this!
403070.drop_descrip: Huh? Why are you staring at me like I'm some weirdo? I'll have you know, it's not like I wanted to do this or anything!
403070.skill: I'll have you pay close attention to my performance!
403070.profile: I'm the mightiest heavy cruiser in the world, Admiral Hipper of the Iron Blood. It's not like I wanted to do this or anything, I just had no say in the matter.
403070.touch2: H-haah?! You did that on purpose, didn't you?!
403070.mission: Mission or offer, it's all the same to me. Let's just get it out of the way!
403070.home: Haah?! You big idiot, you took so long to come back that I was getting worr... Wait, what the heck am I saying?!
403070.win_mvp: If that's the best you can do, I should've just stayed home!
403070.expedition: What are you spacing out for? The commission fleet is back, and you're coming with me!
couple_encourage: You'd better not drag me down!
403070.mail: Huh? Shouldn't you be in charge of vetting the fanmail?!
403070.feeling3: Here, my schedule... Huh?! Look, anyone can do this kind of simple bookkeeping. It's not like I need you or anything!

307012.touch: Commander, you just spoke with that girl, didn't you? Just an "ordinary greeting?" Akagi understands... but if you get even an inch more "ordinary" with her, Akagi can't guarantee what will happen... Ahaha...
307012.login: Welcome back, Commander. Would you like to have dinner, a bath or... ahh, forget about that and eat me up first~
307012.main: Commander, we'll always be together, this year as well~ |Commander, I've finished this batch of paperwork. Is there anything else you'd like me to attend to? Of course, if you're tired, please tell me~
307012.unlock: Commander will always remain by Akagi's side... Right, "Gods?" Of course... Akagi will deal with the pests.... Ahaha...
307012.drop_descrip: Commander will always remain by Akagi's side... Right, "Gods?" Of course... Akagi will deal with the pests.... Ahaha...
307012.touch2: Ahaha... Akagi is always ready and willing~

305026.detail: Milord, Milord, my friends from the other camps taught me all kinds of neat stuff! To thank them, I also taught them about some of our traditional games!
305026.touch: It was so romantic when I bumped into Commander when I turned around the corner... Maybe next time, I'll wait there on purpose... Eek! Ah, um, you didn't hear anything!
305026.login: Milord, here's your bento~ I made it myself!
305026.main: Milord, Milord! I want to start a Miko Club at school to help people better understand the work that Fusou and I do! Um, but right now, we still haven't recruited enough members... |Milord, I only learned this recently, but ship magazines are really complex... Um, I'll study harder, so that nothing bad will happen to mine again! School is so much fun! I wish Fusou could be here with us as well... But, um, wouldn't it make more sense for her to be a teacher?
305026.unlock: Uwaah! M-Milord?! I'm so, so sorry... You didn't get hurt, did you? Um... This is my school uniform. Fusou tailored it for me, hehe~ ... Awawa! I should head off to class now! See you later!
305026.drop_descrip: Uwaah! M-Milord?! I'm so, so sorry... You didn't get hurt, did you? Um... This is my school uniform. Fusou tailored it for me, hehe~ ... Awawa! I should head off to class now! See you later!
305026.home: Good work, Milord! Let's go up to the roof to eat lunch together~

301560.detail: C-Commander, I haven't, um... disappointed you... have I?
301560.touch: Commander? I'm worrying if I did something wrong today... I-I don't think... I have...
301560.login: Commander, I've sorted all your documents... You wanted your documents sorted... right?
301560.battle: A real battle... I'll give it my all...!
301560.feeling2: Commander, is there something you wish me to do? I-is it possible I might have caused you trouble without realizing it?
301560.mission_complete: Commander, I brought the mission rewards. I didn't make another mistake, did I...?
301560.main: I want to be useful to you, Commander, but if I cause you trouble instead... Then what will I do...|If I cause you any trouble, I'll let you touch my ears and my tail, so please don't get mad at me...|For this one you do this, then here you do... this... I think? I-I hope this will work...
301560.feeling5: I'm timid and I often make mistakes, so I doubt I'll ever be very helpful to you, Commander... But I'm okay with that. Because what matters is...
301560.upgrade: Commander, whenever I think about failing to meet your expectations... it almost makes me start crying... *Sob*...
301560.unlock: I'm {namecode:125}, the fifth ship of the {namecode:26}-class. I-I sincerely hope I can be of servish to... *Whimper*... I've made another mistake... Even though I practiced on it so much...
301560.feeling4: Ever since I came to your base, I've started making considerably fewer mistakes... But even when I do, you don't get mad at me, so I've slowly but surely been able to get better... Also, when you encourage me by stroking my ears, your hand feels so warm...
301560.feeling1: I knew I probably wouldn't be of any use to you...
301560.propose: Even if they're a coward, even if they often make mistakes, what matters is telling your partner that you love them from the bottom of your heart, right...? This is the one thing I've believed ever since I was born... Okay, from now on I swear I'll always be with you, Commander...
301560.skill: I-I'm not mistaken here, am I?!
301560.profile: I'm {namecode:125}, I'm the fifth ship of the {namecode:26}-class, I was constructed as part of the Circle Four Plan. But... I might be the least useful ship ever constructed... *Sob*...
301560.touch2: Eek?! C-Commander... you're seriously going to make me cry...
301560.mission: Commander, we have new missions. I'm certain it is a new one. I confirmed it myself...
301560.home: Commander... you're not hurt, are you...?
301560.win_mvp: I hope I didn't cause any trouble for anyone...
301560.expedition: Commander... a commission's been completed... I didn't get the time wrong... did I?
301560.mail: Commander, you have mail... Here... oh, wait, is it this one?
301560.feeling3: I'm trying my best not to cause trouble for people, but I don't know how... So instead I ended up making a lot of mistakes...

101442.detail: Whew! It's freezing cold outside, but warm and cozy in here! Nothing beats an open fireplace in the winter~
101442.touch: Are you feeling chilly? Come a little closer if you wanna warm up, then~
101442.login: I get excited thinking about what kind of presents I might get! What stuff did you wish for, Commander?
101442.main: You'd be surprised how easy wrapping presents is! You just put it like this... take some wrapping paper... then a ribbon... aaand done!|Man, I wish I could ride anywhere in a cool snowmobile like Minneapolis. "It's too dangerous for a kid to ride"? Hey! It's not like I'm a little baby or anything!|I'm getting kinda bored... Hey, Commander, wanna play word association? With a Christmas theme, obviously!
101442.unlock: Hm? I'm just wrapping up some presents! Can't just present them as-is, and all that. Hehe~ I could sure use a little help, Commander!
101442.drop_descrip: Hm? I'm just wrapping up some presents! Can't just present them as-is, and all that. Hehe~ I could sure use a little help, Commander!
101442.touch2: Hrmph... You're not fooling me with any "just wanted to warm my hands up" excuses!
101442.home: I'm not sure who'll end up getting this snowglobe, but I am sure they'll love it!
101442.expedition: I think the commission team's back. Let's invite them in here and we can all have a cozy Christmas together!
101442.mail: New mail, huh? You think it might be someone's Christmas wishlist?

101310.detail: Zzzz... Oh, C-Commander? Are you gonna say that I've been slacking off too much and now I have to sortie?!
101310.login: I'm different from you, Commander. I'd prefer to just stay here and not go anywhere else...
101310.battle: ... We came here to win... right?
101310.feeling2: I'm not sleepy... I just can't open my eyes.
101310.mission_complete: Commander, since we're done for now, do you think I could...
101310.main: Sakura Empire torpedoes... that's scary stuff...|Commander, how about you learn from Helena and just leave me to my own devices?|I really don't feel like training... not at all...
101310.feeling5: *Yawns*... Well, if I stay in your room, I can look at you and sleep at the same time, Commander...
101310.unlock: I'm Nicholas, the first Fletcher-class ship to be launched... I'd rather stay at the base than head out to battle... You don't mind, right?
101310.feeling4: If I always stay in my room then I won't get to see you much, Commander... Hmm, what should I do...
101310.feeling1: I'm never leaving my room... Never!
101310.propose: *Groans*... How long is this ceremony going to last... I want to go back and sleep... Don't you agree, Commander?
101310.drop_descrip: Fletcher-class destroyer – Nicholas, Hull Number DD-449!
101310.profile: I'm Nicholas, DD-449... Although my hull number is at the bottom of the list, I was actually the first Fletcher-class to be commissioned and launched... I mainly provided fire support, and... I contributed to the sinking of Jintsuu and the rescue of Helena, but I don't have much else noteworthy to my name... If there is nothing else you want to know, can I go back?
101310.mission: It's not like we HAVE to finish our missions... right?
101310.home: W-welcome back, Commander! ... Hey, listen, can I leave already?
101310.win_mvp: Guess I'm the MVP... That's unusual.
101310.expedition: The commission team is back... I'm heading back now too...
couple_encourage: Helena, keep an eye out for what's hidden under the water!
101310.mail: We invented email for a reason...
101310.feeling3: C-Commander, if you're free, then how about coming to my room and playing some games...?
101310.lose: I-I really should've never left the base...

808011.detail: This scooter really is fantastic! A good buy for a good price~ Lucky me♪
808011.touch: Oh, you finally noticed, Commander! That's right, I put my hair up just for today's ride! This is your only chance to see it like this.
808011.login: Commander, are you ready? Then we're off to the next stop~
808011.main: Commander, you can give me puppy-dog eyes all you want, but I won't share my ice cream... F-fine, just one lick, got it? |My twin-gun turrets are also on vacation today! Gotta work hard and play hard! |Uhh, I don't think I'll bring the puppy with me next time... He's way too jumpy and almost even fell off the scooter once...
808011.feeling5: Here, Commander. You drive and I'll hold onto you from behind like this~ Mmm, now it feels like we're a real couple~ I've always wanted to try it out myself♪
808011.unlock: Hmm? Commander, are you shopping as well? If so, why don't you come along and take a look around? ... Huh? Of course you can't climb on. That'd be illegal.
808011.drop_descrip: Hmm? Commander, are you shopping as well? If so, why don't you come along and take a look around? ... Huh? Of course you can't climb on. That'd be illegal.
808011.touch2: I can't believe you. You almost made me drop my ice cream!

305029.detail: Milord~ Was I able to be of use to you?
305029.touch: Milord! Milord! Did you know? I used new bath salts last night~!
305029.main: If I can be of use to you, Milord, I'll do anything...|Milord! Milord! I think I've gotten faster! Did you notice? Uu... I'll... try harder...|With my flying friends around, I won't need to light fires with my main cannons to cook anymore~!
305029.unlock: Milord! I can do anything now~ bombardment or aerial strikes! So, the thing is, you can totally count on me, much much more, Milord! Milord~!
305029.drop_descrip: Milord! I can do anything now~ bombardment or aerial strikes! So, the thing is, you can totally count on me, much much more, Milord! Milord~!
305029.touch2: Ahh!! Milord, watch out! My seaplanes are going to run into you!!

307023.detail: Have you finished making your rounds? As I said, we can always catch up later. There are many others who are still waiting for your words... But since you're already here, might as well take a break if you want a change of pace.
307023.touch: You wanna kill some time? Hmph. Very well, how about a round of chess then? I've been wanting to see how your powers have developed... Hehehe...
307023.login: It's time for the star of tonight's show, huh? ...Don't worry, I'll cover for you even if you mess up.
307023.main: Zuikaku, find some way to keep Taihou busy. Can't do much about her clinging to the commander, but there's going to be trouble if Akagi sees her.|The weak shouldn't push past their limits. You certainly don't want to end up like Yorktown over there.|It's not that I don't want to attend the party. If I'm to keep tabs on everything going on, this is the best place to do that from.
307023.unlock: This statue seems to have been inspired by the teachings of the Iris Orthodoxy. Though I am unfamiliar with this kind of art, gazing upon such majesty... fills one with a sense of piety. Commander, can you feel it as well?
307023.drop_descrip: This statue seems to have been inspired by the teachings of the Iris Orthodoxy. Though I am unfamiliar with this kind of art, gazing upon such majesty... fills one with a sense of piety. Commander, can you feel it as well?
307023.home: A victory, huh? As Akagi's... as my sister's partner, anything less would render you unfit for that honor.
307023.win_mvp: This is the judgment exacted upon the weak by the strong. Live on so that you may forever choke on the bitterness of defeat!
307023.expedition: The girls of the commission fleet have returned. Shall I bring some refreshments out to them?

808012.detail: Sure, I go in the water all the time since I'm a submarine, but it's nice to just relax by the beach every now and then! *yaaaawn*... A girl needs her vacation time, you know~
808012.touch: You're head over heels for my gorgeous body, aren't you? Heheh, stare all you want, because I don't mind♡
808012.login: Hey, Commander, done anything fun lately? I wanna know!
808012.main: Hey, Commander! Just lie on your back and I'll cover you with sand~|Go get the camera, Commander! I wanna take a photo of this.|Passepartout, could you get me some sunscreen? Oh, and Commander, would you mind rubbing it on for me?
808012.unlock: Mmmh~ Bonjour, Commander~ Nothing feels better than the waves lapping at your skin~ Oh, Commander, why don't you come lie down and experience it for yourself?
808012.drop_descrip: Mmmh~ Bonjour, Commander~ Nothing feels better than the waves lapping at your skin~ Oh, Commander, why don't you come lie down and experience it for yourself?
808012.home: Welcome back, Comma– Whuah! Geesh, that last wave was huge! You could've warned me that it was coming! Hmph!

403043.detail: What belongs to my lowly animal also belongs to me. Therefore, the stronger my lowly animal's fleet is, the clearer the proof of my excellence is.
403043.touch: Dancing? Aha~ I just knew you'd come to me with this request, so I prac... err, prepared beforehand!
403043.login: Still sluggish as always. But because I'm in a pretty decent mood today, I'll forgive you!
403043.mission_complete: Hmph... After seeing these rewards, I'll let you live.
403043.main: Lowly animal, you may offer your opinion about me and Graf Spee's dresses. Hmph, I bet your vocabulary doesn't include anything beyond "cute," ahahaha! |Ehh? Graf Spee is actually talking to people from other factions...? I hope she's not being bullied... I'll have to give them a stern warning just in case... |Tell me, lowly animal, why does everyone greet me instead of cowering in fear? ...Because they like me? R-really... Hmph. As a spiritual leader, it's only natural to be respected by all!
403043.unlock: I seem pleased? Of course I am. Why wouldn't I be when my sweet little sister will be joining us at the party? Now shape up and entertain your master, you lowly animal! Ahahahaha!
403043.drop_descrip: I seem pleased? Of course I am. Why wouldn't I be when my sweet little sister will be joining us at the party? Now shape up and entertain your master, you lowly animal! Ahahahaha!
403043.mission: Missions? What mission could possibly be more important than accompanying your master to the banquet?
403043.home: Let's be clear here, I was not waiting for you. I simply can't show off the full extent of my grandeur as a master without the presence of my lowly animal.
403043.win_mvp: You should feel honored to have the privilege of being ravaged by the one-and-only Deutschland while she is in a good mood!
403043.mail: Getting mail right now sure spoils the mood. Let me see those!
403043.lose: I have a banquet to attend, so I have no time to let myself get dragged through the mud by you lot~

305028.detail: Milord, how was my Kaguya dance? Fusou taught me this dance to help get rid of bad luck!
305028.touch: Milord, I want to touch you as well! *Rub rub~ pat pat~*!
305028.login: Milord, welcome back... Wooooah! Ehehe... I've lost track of the number of times you've had to catch me~
305028.main: Milord, let me help clean your ears! |Milord, when spring comes around, let's go view the cherry blossoms! |Milord, want to take a nap in Yamashiro's lap?
305028.feeling5: Milord, I love you more than anything else! Being with you is so fun and joyous! I want to stay together with you forever and ever, Milord!
305028.unlock: Milord, Milord, I've finished changing! What do you think? Do you like Yamashiro's new outfit?
305028.drop_descrip: Milord, Milord, I've finished changing! What do you think? Do you like Yamashiro's new outfit?
305028.touch2: Milord, you can get lovey-dovey with Yamashiro all you want! Mmhmm!
305028.home: Milord, Milord, come rest here for a while! Yamashiro will give you a massage... hup!

301058.detail: Now, I know that I'm not alone anymore... because you're here after all, Commander...
301058.touch: Commander, I like cuddling with you like this... It feels nice.
301058.login: No matter where you go, Ayanami shall always walk three steps behind you. Commander... shall we go?
301058.main: I'm not sure... I understand the meaning of these clothes... but since you'd like me to wear them, I don't mind... |Everyone was staring at me so excitedly... I'm not used to this... |
301058.feeling5: I enjoy being with everyone, but... I'd also like to spend more time alone with you, Commander...
301058.unlock: I'm still... your Ayanami... though I'm not very used to this outfit... Commander, does it suit me?
301058.drop_descrip: I'm still... your Ayanami... though I'm not very used to this outfit... Commander, does it suit me?
301058.touch2: This feels... a bit weird after all... But, if you like it, I don't mind...
301058.home: Commander... shall I rub your shoulders?
301058.win_mvp: Commander, as long as you're by my side, I won't lose.

901030.detail: Oh gosh! D-don't just appear outta nowhere, Commander... You'll scare people.
901030.touch: What's up? Need me to do you a favor?
901030.login: So, Commander, didn't you promise you'd return with snacks for me? Uhh, what? We never made any promise like that?
901030.battle: Witness the true might of a LARGE destroyer!
901030.hp_warning: Stay calm and wait for the right time...!
901030.feeling2: I got one of Miss Dunkerque's cakes! Oh boy, which one is it today? Think you could guess, Commander?
901030.mission_complete: Holy cow! Look, Commander! We got a huge bounty for that mission! O-oh, it's nothing out of the ordinary?
901030.main: You look bored and in need of some relief, Commander. Perchance you would fancy a showcase of my lancing skill– Oh gosh, careful! You'll get hurt!|Can I ask you a favor, Commander? Well, I was hoping you could, uhh... leave out the bell peppers from my dinner tonight...|Aah, so it's like that, huh. I understand everything now. Let me take it on... NOT!
901030.feeling5: Plus, when you're playing dumb, you don't need to use your brain! It's refreshing to just not think about anything! Thus, when you enjoy yourself, others will, too! You should give it a try sometime, Commander!
901030.upgrade: You're not gonna... dump additional work on me now, are you?
901030.unlock: Tadaah! Nameship of the Vauquelin-class large destroyers, Vauquelin, has arrived in style! Hey, what's so funny? I may not look strong, but I am! Um, probably!
901030.feeling4: Whether I'm actually dumb or not doesn't matter, but sometimes I like pretending to be stupid. Then when I do something smart, people are gonna be like, "Whoa, you're a genius, Vauquelin!" That's how it goes! I mean... it does, right?
901030.feeling1: You know, I've learned something, Commander. People who can't introspect probably won't make many friends...
901030.propose: Holy smokes... You really meant that thing the other day about getting married?! Well, not to say I took it as a joke, or didn't believe you, or anything... Uhh, I mean... Y-you get what I'm trying to say, right...?
901030.profile: (I wanna give a cool self-introduction, but I don't have many exploits to my name... I did escort Dunkerque and Algérie, though that's not much...) Long story short: I'm Vauquelin from the Vichya Dominion! I've got more potential than you can imagine! C-cool, am I right?
901030.touch2: You're making me a bit uncomfortable, Commander...
901030.mission: A mission, you say? Hehehe! Finally, it's my time to shine!
901030.home: For all your hard work, you deserve a headpat... Whuah! Spare me that expression of yours!
901030.win_mvp: MVP! This calls for a celebratory cool pose... Uhh, why's everyone giving me funny looks?
901030.expedition: A commission's complete! Just F-Y-I! So yeah, let's go receive the returning team.
couple_encourage: So Tartu, did you finish that book I lent you the other day?
901030.mail: Mail? Oh, I'll go get it then!
901030.feeling3: Something that's bothered me lately? Well, Tartu asked me for advice on becoming more ladylike, so I thoughtlessly recommended this detective novel I've been reading, and she apparently got hooked on reading it... It feels like that was a mistake, you know?
901030.lose: Huh? You're asking for my opinion on what went wrong? Dunno, that's your job to find out, Commander!

403042.detail: Lazy swine, don't cut corners. Anything less than a perfectly uniform application of sunscreen is unacceptable!
403042.touch: To think that a plebeian would look at me with such a hungry, bestial expression. A lewd beast like this needs a thorough flogging.
403042.login: Way! Too! Slow! Are you trying to get my pristine skin sunburnt?
403042.main: Plebeian, fetch those two towels over there and wipe my body dry. |If your eyes wander any lower, they will get detached from their sockets. I say, there is no remedy for being uncultured swine~ |A lifebuoy? What would I use that for? Plebeian, were you not going to carry me on your back while swimming?
403042.unlock: One must not neglect sunscreen during the summer... Plebeian, if you wish to serve your master, prostrate yourself and yell "I beg of you, Queen Deutschland" three times, and I might consider giving you an opportunity. Ahahaha~
403042.drop_descrip: One must not neglect sunscreen during the summer... Plebeian, if you wish to serve your master, prostrate yourself and yell "I beg of you, Queen Deutschland" three times, and I might consider giving you an opportunity. Ahahaha~
403042.touch2: Ho ho, it looks like this lowly swine cannot even control its basest desires.
403042.home: What's with that lax expression of yours as soon as you get back... Ho ho, do you need your master to "tighten up" those loose morals of yours?

205011.detail: We shall allow you to bask in our splendor! ... Now out with your praise already! Lowly servant!
205011.touch: Hm, hmph! ... Considering the lengths to which you went for this party, we shall overlook your boorishness for now. Be grateful for your queen's leniency! Lowly servant!
205011.main: So as not to embarrass me at the party, you need to practice your dancing! Y-you could practice with m-... You don't want to bother me?! B-b-but it really wouldn't be much trouble!|It is a servant's duty to clear the way for the Queen, are we clear?!|Bel! Is everything ready for the party? N-not that I'm excited about it or anything! I'm just supervising my maids!
