205011.unlock: Hah haah! You're a lucky servant this evening! We shall allow you to accompany us to the party! ... B-but it's not like I chose you because I like you! I just... Yes! I just sort of chose randomly! Got it?!
205011.drop_descrip: Hah haah! You're a lucky servant this evening! We shall allow you to accompany us to the party! ... B-but it's not like I chose you because I like you! I just... Yes! I just sort of chose randomly! Got it?!
205011.touch2: Aie! Warspite!! Level your fifteen-inch guns at this insolent servant! Off with its heeaaaaaad!!

305039.touch: You interested in my flight deck?
305039.login: Commander, my guns are gonna rust up if you keep me in port forever.
305039.main: Damn... Guess aviation battleships can't fly, after all. Kinda let down, honestly...|What? I can't let my aircraft fly around the port whenever I want? Why not?!|Phew... What a nice day! Maybe I'll call over Hyuuga later so we can all go for some drinks. Whaddya say, Commander?
305039.unlock: Planes: check! Main guns: check! Nobody can stop me now! Let's sortie right now, Commander! I'm fired up and wanna wreak some havoc on the battlefield!
305039.drop_descrip: Planes: check! Main guns: check! Nobody can stop me now! Let's sortie right now, Commander! I'm fired up and wanna wreak some havoc on the battlefield!
305039.touch2: Aviation battleships can't fly, but if you want me to send you flying, then I'll grant your wish.
305039.home: Keep an eye out? My aircraft can do that, easy peasy. I tell ya, these beauts are really handy~

901032.detail: Wow, rude much, Commander and Tartu? Way to fall asleep during my performance! ...I mean, technically I wasn't personally performing... But still!
901032.touch: Got any requests? Like a song, or food, or even a thrilling chat with yours truly? Hehehe~
901032.login: Check it out! Your favorite Vauquelin, now in a fancy dress! Also, good luck at work, Commander!
901032.battle: Let us play a requiem! ...Hang on, that sounds familiar...
901032.main: Gotta swing in rhythm to the music, like... Oh, Commander! Guess what? I've been getting tons of compliments on my conducting skills! Hehehe~!|Right-o! Now'd be a good time for a relaxing song! ...Wake up, Commander! You're sleeping on the job!|
901032.unlock: Yes, the strings... I can hear the celebratory melody... Now, follow my lead and we'll take this song to greater– Oh, Commander? What's all this, you ask? Uhh... You know... Ahahaha...
901032.drop_descrip: Yes, the strings... I can hear the celebratory melody... Now, follow my lead and we'll take this song to greater– Oh, Commander? What's all this, you ask? Uhh... You know... Ahahaha...
901032.touch2: Bet you were imagining these were Tartu's knockers. Hmph.
901032.win_mvp: First place! Let's hear a victory song for me! Wait a sec... Where'd my orchestra go?
901032.lose: So yeah, I'm thinking it's time for me to scoot! Phew... Good thing I picked a non-cumbersome dress...

204020.detail: Hi, Commander! I changed into something a little easier to move around in~
204020.touch: Huh? I thought you'd be into softer girls than me...
204020.login: Hello, Commander! Let's go beat the heck out of our enemies!
204020.battle: Vaporize anything that moves into ash!
204020.feeling2: It's so boring indoors! Being outdoors is so much better... Commander, don't you feel bad sitting around all day? Let's go out and get some fresh air!
204020.main: Hey! Com~man~der~! Let's get some exercise~!|You look strong, Commander. Want to spar sometime?|Huh? You think I'm impatient?
204020.feeling5: You know, Commander, I am a girl after all. I'm not so crazy I'd defencelessly cling to someone I don't like. It's about time you noticed...
204020.upgrade: Commander, want to go take a stroll out to sea? I'll protect you!
204020.unlock: I'm Repulse, a Renown-class battlecruiser. I participated in the pursuit of Bismarck, but we couldn't catch up to her. Ever since then I've been a part of Force Z... I don't ever want to see a torpedo again...
204020.feeling4: Com~man~der! Gotcha! Hmm? I'm too close? Hey, what's the problem with that~ Anyway, come and play with me~!
204020.feeling1: It's kinda boring being here with you... I'm heading out for a while!
204020.propose: Huh?! You're happy with me? I'm not as elegant as some other royal girls, and I don't dress all that great... But when it comes to my feelings for you, I rank second to none!
204020.profile: I'm Repulse, a Renown-class battlecruiser. I may not look like much, but I've been tons of places with the higher-ups! Though I prefer going out on my own! "Repairs"? Ahahaha, I'm hoping you won't keep me locked up indoors every day, Commander...
204020.touch2: Whoah! S-stop… You're awful! I'm a girl, you know!
204020.home: You can't rest right after reaching port! Go exercise more!
204020.win_mvp: Hooray! We won! Quick, decisive victories are my favourite.
204020.expedition: You've made me stay with you inside, so, as your punishment, you'll have to accompany me to check up on the completed commissions. Let's go!
204020.mail: Deliverygirl Repulse has arrived with your mail!
204020.feeling3: My sister always says I'm too impatient, but I can't be bothered thinking everything through. Besides, you're always around, so I'll leave all the thinking to you, Commander!
204020.lose: Ahh, the enemy was so persistent that I'm starving now... There's no way we could've won like this...

307024.drop_descrip: I never thought you'd end up taking such a long trip with me just to pick up a dress... Though I'm worried about leaving my sister behind at port, I suppose I should take your advice and relax a bit.

403044.detail: The decor in here is truly sumptuous... Hahahah! It further raises the pedestal of eminence atop which I sit! Isn't that right, lowly animal? Ahahahaha!
403044.touch: Are you trying to touch my stole? I have no memory of granting a lowly animal permission to do that!
403044.login: There you are, lowly animal. Now help me take off these heels! Strolling around in these things is so tiresome...
403044.main: If Spee wasn't so dear to me, I would've never even *considered* building a snowman!|Oh lowly animal, your master is hungry. I've heard that the Dragon Empery's cuisine is very delectable... You know what to do now, yes? Ahahahahah!|So much noise... Oh lowly animal, go outside and check what happened!
403044.unlock: Why are so many people out and about during a holiday? ...That's it! Lowly animal, was it your idea to prepare all this to surprise me...?! Heh... Hehe, that's right, don't you dare disappoint me!
403044.drop_descrip: Why are so many people out and about during a holiday? ...That's it! Lowly animal, was it your idea to prepare all this to surprise me...?! Heh... Hehe, that's right, don't you dare disappoint me!
403044.touch2: Hahah, do you yearn for my punishment that badly, lowly animal?
403044.home: You lowly animal! For how long do you intend to ignore me?!

10100060.detail: Hey... Don't you think you're a bit too close?
10100060.touch: W-wait... suddenly touching me like that... of course I'd be shocked!
10100060.login: I'll show you how a CPU fights! I'm ready whenever you are.
10100060.battle: Let's give it our all from the very start!
10100060.feeling2: Hey... do you have any friends? Hmm... as a special service, I wouldn't object to becoming your friend.
10100060.mission_complete: Seems that a mission has been completed. It's only natural to get rewarded for one's hard work.
10100060.main: Commander, isn't that enough training? From now on, let me prove my worth in actual combat.|I was just thinking... the ocean sure is beautiful, isn't it? Why don't we go for a swim to clear our minds?|You sure are spaced out. I wouldn't be opposed to helping lift your spirits, you know.
10100060.feeling5: Even though I'm often harsh with you, I don't really mean it that way... But even then, I might have already hurt you. This time, though, I'd like you to scold me... If it's you, I might be able to change for the better.
10100060.upgrade: Don't think that I'd be satisfied with just this achievement.
10100060.unlock: I'm the CPU of Lastation, Black Heart. I've rushed here all the way from Gamindustri to lend you my aid. Be grateful.
10100060.feeling4: It seems like we understand each other a lot better now. At first, I thought you'd give up halfway, but you've certainly changed a little. Let's work hard together and continue to grow from now.
10100060.feeling1: You should know what will happen if you try to get any closer.
10100060.propose: Are you sure about choosing me? This is the only time you'll get to change your mind... I see... so your answer is still the same. Well, it's not like I particularly like you that much or anything, but if you're this serious, I'll have to give you an equally serious reply. But... if you're going to cop out on me, I won't forgive you!
10100060.drop_descrip: I'm the CPU of Lastation, Black Heart. I've rushed here all the way from Gamindustri to lend you my aid. Be grateful.
10100060.profile: I am Black Heart, the CPU and guardian of Lastation. Be sure to properly learn from my refined combat techniques.
10100060.touch2: Even if you're the commander... I won't allow you to go any further.
10100060.mission: It seems that new missions have been posted. Let's hurry up and knock these out.
10100060.home: I've safely returned to port. Now then, let's report the battle results and begin debriefing.
10100060.expedition: Looks like a commission's been completed. Hurry and take a look.
couple_encourage: I won't forgive you if you drag me down!
Can you withstand this attack？
10100060.mail: Looks like you have some new mail. If you're busy, I wouldn't object to getting it for you...
10100060.feeling3: Looks like you've been hard at work. Since I happen to be free right now, why don't I help you out?
10100060.lose: So this is the bitterness of defeat? However.... next time, I'll win for sure.

301309.touch: Aren't you a needy commander. You require my assistance, do you, now?
301309.main: I went for a romp with some of those Mutsuki-class children, but they proved no more than a bothersome bunch of pipsqueaks.|My wind chime? It quite strikes my fancy, though it is a bit too large. Watch yourself so you don't get whacked by it!|Ah, Haguro, Ashigara, and Myoukou... How I miss the days of watching over those younglings~
301309.unlock: Ohohoho, you must have a sharp eye if you've decided to retrofit me~ Now that I've been chosen, I cannot afford to embarrass you. Now, take a good and thorough look at this veteran's aspirations~
301309.drop_descrip: Ohohoho, you must have a sharp eye if you've decided to retrofit me~ Now that I've been chosen, I cannot afford to embarrass you. Now, take a good and thorough look at this veteran's aspirations~
301309.win_mvp: Being in the first Destroyer Division and being the first of my class, it's only natural I also get first place!

10100070.login: So damn slow... Ugh. How long are you gonna keep me waiting?
10100070.battle: Don't think you can go home just like this!
10100070.hp_warning: You little shits are making me mad!
10100070.feeling2: Oi, where are you looking, you bastard? You don't need to answer, I already know! ...You think I'm cute? Flattery isn't going to get you anywhere.
10100070.main: How long do I have to keep waiting here? My tech is gonna go obsolete at this rate.|Am I angry? ... It's just how I talk, don't worry about it.|Don't worry. I'll protect you.
10100070.feeling5: Don't worry, I'll always be at your side. I'm not sure why but, I always feel like my chest is hot and overflowing with power.
10100070.unlock: I'm White Heart, the guardian CPU of Lowee. Pleased to meet you. I'm gonna give you a taste of a CPU's power!
10100070.feeling4: Yo, Commander! Next time, let's go out somewhere! By the way, you have no right to refuse.
10100070.feeling1: I don't want to see your sorry mug at all!
10100070.propose: This is... for me? Are you for real? I see... so you are. Understood, I'll accept your feelings. I'll become even stronger, so I can continue to be your shield!
10100070.drop_descrip: I'm White Heart, the guardian CPU of Lowee. Pleased to meet you. I'm gonna give you a taste of a CPU's power!
10100070.skill: I'm gonna beat you into tatters!
10100070.profile: I'm the CPU of Lowee, White Heart. I have two little sisters. Although they are mischievous prankers and a handful to look after, they're still very cute. Next time, why don't we all play together?
10100070.mission: Hurry up and take care of these missions.
10100070.home: That was a pretty good battle, wasn't it? Let's keep it up just like this.
10100070.win_mvp: Did I hold back too much?
10100070.expedition: A commission team has returned. Why don't we welcome them back?
couple_encourage: Hey, Green Heart! Get those giant Thunder Tits outta here, I can't even see in front of me!
Forward, everyone! Prepare yourselves!
10100070.mail: Yo, the mail's here. Hurry up and take a look.
10100070.feeling3: Even though you're an unreliable commander, I still have some expectations for you.
10100070.lose: If you hold me back again... I'll end you.

10100040.detail: Ohoho, do you have business with me?
10100040.touch: Ohoho, you're quite the mischief-maker, aren't you?
10100040.login: Good day. I was just about to brew some tea. Would you like to have some together with me, Commander?
10100040.battle: Commander, are you prepared for this?
10100040.hp_warning: It is just as I thought; the enemy is no match for me.
10100040.feeling2: Would you like to play an MMO together with me? Yes, of course I will assist you with everything you need to know!
10100040.mission_complete: Mission completed! Let us go collect our rewards!
10100040.main: Ohoho, I will watch over you, Commander. You may rest assured and know that I can guarantee your safety.|Ohhh?! Tell me, what is that girl's name?! Please, I beg you, let me make her my little sister!|I feel completely overjoyed that there are so many cute little girls here.
10100040.feeling5: Being with you warms my heart, like a hot cup of tea. And just as I love tea, I love you. I want this moment in time to last forever, but perhaps that makes me sound selfish...?
10100040.upgrade: I shall set my sights even higher.
10100040.unlock: My name is Vert, I am the CPU of Leanbox. I'm very good at first-person shooters, so please let me handle all combat-related matters!
10100040.feeling4: May I ask you for some advice, Commander? There's a person who I've recently grown quite fond of, but I don't know how I should approach him... On second thought, never mind I said anything!
10100040.feeling1: Could I just return home to Leanbox?
10100040.propose: So you wish to drink my tea till death do us apart, I see...? That makes me so happy. I will gladly make tea to just your liking, my commander... no, my sweetheart.
10100040.drop_descrip: My name is Vert, I am the CPU of Leanbox. I'm very good at first-person shooters, so please let me handle all combat-related matters!
10100040.skill: Witness the glorious power of Leanbox's CPU!
10100040.profile: My name is Vert, I am the CPU of Leanbox. My favorite things are tea, video games, and my adorable little sisters! ...Hm? I have no little sisters, you say? If I view someone as my little sister then they ARE my little sister!
10100040.touch2: If you don't treat women delicately then they will grow tired of you very fast.
10100040.mission: Even just 5 minutes is plenty of time for you to finish a mission, no?
10100040.home: Thank you for your hard work. Now it is time for some tea.
10100040.win_mvp: There is no entry for "defeat" in my lexicon.
10100040.expedition: It seems everyone was able to make it back. Let us give them a warm welcome.
couple_encourage: I think books and tea go hand in hand. May I offer you a cup?
You will regret the day the you decided to make us your enemy!
Once we come back home I will give you all a big hug!
10100040.mail: It would appear mail has arrived. I suggest that you check for it regularly.
10100040.feeling3: I would like to hold a meetup for fellow MMO enthusiasts today! Surely you will be part of it, Commander? I will move forward under the premise that you and I will be in attendance.
10100040.lose: So this is how defeat feels... I see. That battle was so enjoyable that it made my heart race.

10100050.detail: If you're so interested in me, why don't you come closer?
10100050.touch: Ahh...! Listen, if you want my attention then you could just ask for it.
10100050.login: Welcome back. Shall we sortie? Do some exercise battles? Or perhaps... have some pudding?
10100050.battle: I will destroy every last one of them.
10100050.hp_warning: I am Purple Heart and I will not be looked down on!
10100050.feeling2: Such nice weather today. Do you know of any places in this world worth visiting?
10100050.mission_complete: Mission completed. I'm curious about what rewards we'll receive.
10100050.main: I am relieved everyone here is so kind. I will have no issue fighting with all my strength.|I could really use something to drink... Would there happen to be any custard pudding around here?|Oh, Commander? Could you tell me something I should know about your world?
10100050.feeling5: I've grown accustomed to this world, and it's all thanks to you. So, grab my hand and come with me! I say we go on a date for a little while.
10100050.upgrade: To protect the commander and everyone I know... I have to become even stronger.
10100050.unlock: I am Purple Heart, the CPU of Planeptune. You must be the commander. I will follow your orders from now on.
10100050.feeling4: I don't know why but recently I've been unable to concentrate when I'm playing games with you. Is this what it feels like to... Just to make sure you'll have to play with me some more!
10100050.feeling1: I never thought you would disappoint me this badly...
10100050.propose: I see the time has finally come. I'd grown so tired of waiting! Do you understand what giving this to me means? It means you will be my partner in gaming from this day onward. I'm looking forward to it, Commander.
10100050.drop_descrip: I am Purple Heart, the CPU of Planeptune. And you must be the commander. I will follow your orders from now.
10100050.skill: Feel the power of a CPU!
10100050.profile: I'm Purple Heart, the CPU of Planeptune. People always tell me they're amazed by how different I am in HDD form. How rude. This form is exhausting to be in, so I don't transform unless I have to.
10100050.touch2: You're awfully assertive, I see. Do keep the time and place in mind, though.
10100050.mission: Missions, huh... It seems the things a commander and a CPU do are not so different.
10100050.home: That was a splendid workout. How about some time to take a break?
10100050.expedition: The commission team has returned. Should I offer them some assistance?
couple_encourage: I'm leaving that one to you!
Everyone, get ready! Let's make them understand the might of a CPU!
10100050.mail: It seems some mail addressed to you has arrived. You should read it now before you forget to.
10100050.feeling3: Oh, it's you. You came at just the right time. There's a stage I can't clear in this game and I was hoping you could help me with it.

The 18th DesDiv... will come home safely this time.
301810.mail: It'd be nice if Foo could get the mail...
301810.feeling3: Commander, Foo and Kasumi will always stay by yourside, because you're our friend.
301810.lose: Foo, make sure to... protect the others.

403051.detail: I'm trying hard to learn about everyday things. Living a normal life is not so simple, compared to fighting...
403051.touch: Deutschland? Could you stop using your megaphone to shout "people who harass the girl with my phone will be expelled"... It's embarrassing, and more importantly, it's really distracting...
403051.login: Eugen taught me how to use makeup, but... does it actually make me look pretty...?
403051.battle: Don't go around disturbing the girls at the academy.
403051.main: My pantyhose? Ajax gave me them as an enrollment gift... I examined them very thoroughly and didn't find anything weird, but I doubt they're just a normal pair of stockings...|Viersechs doesn't like picture books? I see... Everyone else in the Z-class seems to like them, though...|Hipper? Want some snacks? I get it. "Not really" means "yes" in your dictionary. Okay, say "aah."
403051.feeling5: Does getting a hug from me like this cheer you up a little, Commander?
403051.unlock: I sailed alone, fought alone, and then I was sunk while being alone. Now I found a new beginning... Hmm? Commander, you've been staring and laughing at me since the beginning… do you want to eat this?
403051.drop_descrip: I sailed alone, fought alone, and then I was sunk while being alone. Now I found a new beginning... Hmm? Commander, you've been staring and laughing at me since the beginning… do you want to eat this?
403051.mail: This mail... it's not another one of Ajax's pranks, is it?!

331052.detail: I've inspected the voicechat equipment. It won't cause any more problems...
331052.touch: Is this gamer fuel for me? Thank you.
331052.login: Do you want to play co-op, Commander? Okay. First, you must take this controller.
331052.main: If Ayanami dies... the fate of the villagers falls upon... the ghost gamer...|I have a feeling Little Bel is the best gamer among the Royal Maids...|Could you turn up the AC, please? If the room stays this hot, Ayanami will evaporate...|Oh no! Commander, it's a trap! Good thing we managed to avoid it.
331052.unlock: No, Ryuujou! Samurai builds should stay back during the boss! ...Oh, welcome, Commander. I'm busy with this game right now, so just make yourself at home or something.
331052.drop_descrip: No, Ryuujou! Samurai builds should stay back during the boss! ...Oh, welcome, Commander. I'm busy with this game right now, so just make yourself at home or something.
331052.home: Well done on that battle. Ayanami has a "battle" to return to as well.

703010.detail: No matter how many of my cannons are disabled, even should I get turned into a floating turret, as long as I am still able to fight, I shall fight until my last breath. That is my duty and my obligation.
703010.touch: What do you need? Don't even think about making me do grunt work just because I'm your secretary.
703010.login: You're astonishingly late. Did you want me to discipline you that badly?
703010.battle: Imbeciles! Stop the pointless struggling and surrender!
703010.hp_warning: Urgh... What kind of monsters are they?!
703010.feeling2: If you want me to follow your orders, then prove yourself a capable commander first. I can handle myself if you can't.
703010.headtouch: Wha...?! Keep your hands off my head!
703010.mission_complete: Hello? Confirm the mission rewards. Don't keep us waiting forever.
703010.main: Focus on your work. ...What, you need a break? If you've got the energy to complain, you've got the energy to work.|How do Tashkent and Murmansk manage to fit in with the others so well... What? Nothing important. Focus on your work.|I think I'll have a beer after work. Vodka? No thanks. I'll pass.
703010.feeling5: Are you sure you're fit to be a commander, considering how you take orders from your secretary? Don't worry, I'll keep telling you what to do so you can keep your job. I've started enjoying it, actually. Hehehe~
703010.unlock: The name's Tallinn, heavy cruiser from the Northern Parliament. Don't expect me to blindly take orders from you just because you're the commander. Use that head of yours to think things through first, then we'll talk.
703010.feeling4: I'm surprised you've actually taken my scoldings to heart. Hehe, hahaha... Since you like it when I tell you what to do, I'll be more exact from now on.
703010.feeling1: Use your head before ordering me around. If you can't even do that much, then I won't lift a finger for you.
703010.propose: All you need to do is sign this document, and I'll take care of everything else. Now to put on the ring and make it official with a kiss... So, how did my lips feel? Hehe~♪
703010.skill: Fire all cannons! Don't stop shooting!
703010.profile: I'm Tallinn, Northern Parliament heavy cruiser, formerly known as Lützow under the Iron Blood. I fought in the war under the name of Petropavlovsk as well. In the end, I never did get to unleash my full potential, but I trust your commanding to make good use of me.
703010.mission: It is imperative that missions be completed. This was true during my time in the Iron Blood, and is still true now.
703010.home: Good work out there. Keep it up.
703010.win_mvp: Look at that, we won. Victory comes naturally if you just follow what you trained for.
703010.expedition: Your job now is to go and show your gratitude to the returning commission team. Do it well and in a timely fashion.
couple_encourage: Kirov, I'm counting on you!
Hehe, things are looking pretty good~
I've always thought your name was a little funny.
703010.mail: A letter has come in. I wonder who sent it...
703010.feeling3: Don't like my scoldings? Then do better! You're not about to tell me you actually ENJOY being scolded, I hope.
703010.lose: ...Tsk, all because of some small mistakes...

202161.detail: Hehe, what do you think about my outfit, Commander? Pretty nice, isn't it? ...You don't know where you should be looking? Haha, you cheeky little...
202161.touch: When we're on a date, it's only natural to lock arms and lean against you like this~ Ahaha, are you embarrassed, Commander?
202161.login: Commander, we've talked about the importance of being punctual before, right...? As compensation for making me wait, we're gonna shop 'til we drop! Ahaha!
202161.main: The joy of going shopping is knowing that every time you go out, there's something new to be discovered. Commander, I'll let you handle the "spoils" of our shopping trip. |You've gotta try on some new clothes during your downtime every now and then! Hehe, want me to help you pick out some clothes, Commander? |Girls need to do a lot of preparation before going out, you know? Hair, makeup, clothes, you name it... So, if you want to see us at our cutest, you've got to be patient~
202161.unlock: Did I keep you waiting, Commander? Ahaha... A girl's gotta take her time before stepping out onto the streets, remember? Come on, take my hand, and let's get going! Hehe~
202161.drop_descrip: Did I keep you waiting, Commander? Ahaha... A girl's gotta take her time before stepping out onto the streets, remember? Come on, take my hand, and let's get going! Hehe~
202161.home: Welcome back! Hmm, how are we gonna celebrate your hard work? Ahaha, what do you think about a candle-lit dinner?

101041.detail: Hahahah! Whaddya think of my little creation here? Oh, and don't tell Akashi about it!
101041.touch: What'd I tell you – two heads are more productive than one!
101041.login: Yo! Talk about being early! C'mere and gimme a hand stocking these shelves.
101041.main: Hey, Commander, pass me that triangular can! Cool, thanks!|I reckon I can make an explosive out of stuff lying around the store! ...Look, I'm just saying it's possible!|This fella's almost past its expiration date... Heheh. Should we ask Akashi for permission to do an inventory sweep?
101041.unlock: I heard another person was coming to help out at the store, but I never thought it'd be you, Commander! What am I doing here? Ahaha, well uh, I had a little bit of free time on my hands... right~♪
101041.drop_descrip: I heard another person was coming to help out at the store, but I never thought it'd be you, Commander! What am I doing here? Ahaha, well uh, I had a little bit of free time on my hands... right~♪
101041.home: And this bottle goes ri– Oh crap! ...Phew! Nice catch, Commander! That was a real close one...

403050.detail: No matter how poor the odds are, I will always head for the battlefield. ...That way people will admire me.
403050.touch: It's sunny today? Yeah... just like it was back on the Río de la Plata.
403050.login: I will fight for you till the very end.
403050.battle: For the honor and prosperity of Iron Blood, and for even greater glory!
403050.hp_warning: I have to hold out just a little longer...!
403050.feeling2: I sailed alone, fought alone, and sunk alone... Although I am who I am, didn't I still contribute to Iron Blood's cause?
403050.headtouch: Commander, could you not ruffle up my hair like that...?
403050.mission_complete: I see that, unlike me in the past, you actually finished your mission.
403050.main: Wars don't exist for mindless slaughter, they exist for victory.|One's first battle being their last... That sort of thing isn't all that unusual for us Iron Blood ships.|Give talking to people... a try? I've always been alone, so what am I supposed to talk about...
403050.feeling5: No matter how much I fight, I can't fill the void in my heart... And being away from you is the reason why...
403050.unlock: No matter where I go, the war never ends... Deutschland-class armored ship number 3, Admiral Graf Spee, reporting for duty.
403050.feeling4: Commander, rather than sink all alone, will I be able to face my final moments together with you this time?
403050.feeling1: No matter how you treat me, Commander, I will obey you...
403050.propose: Although I cannot hug you, you can hug me... Hey, Commander, just for a little longer... hold me tight like this...
403050.drop_descrip: Deutschland-class armored cruiser number three – Admiral Graf Spee.
403050.skill: In the name of all that is dear to me!
403050.profile: Admiral Graf Spee, Deutschland-class armored cruiser number 3 of the Iron Blood Navy. I was attacked by Royal Navy cruisers and then took refuge in Montevideo, but in the end I scuttled myself... Commander, this time I'm going to fight! To the very end!
403050.touch2: Commander, may I hug you, even though my hands are like this?
403050.mission: Once we've been assigned a mission, we must complete it, no matter what it is.
403050.home: Commander, you've confirmed the port isn't being blockaded, right?
403050.win_mvp: How long will this victory actually last...
403050.expedition: A commission has been completed? That means they weren't ambushed. Thank goodness.
couple_encourage: Stay away from me...
You're still a dirty sadist, I see.
It's an honor to fight alongside you again.
403050.mail: This letter... Thank goodness, it has nothing to do with Renown.
403050.feeling3: These hands are for grasping victory... Even though I will never again be able to hug the people important to me, what's done is done.
403050.lose: We've lost... But I'm not giving up! It's not over yet!

112011.detail: Although summer is a vacation period for many, Doctor Vestal is in all year round♪
112011.touch: You want to go in the ocean with me...? Hmm, I suppose I should accept your invitation and take a quick dip. But just a quick one, okay~?
112011.login: Commander, please be aware of the risk of heatstroke when at the beach.
112011.battle: The sea breeze is so refreshing, isn't it~
112011.main: I'll stay here and watch over everyone, so you go on ahead into the ocean, Commander~ Now, now, don't be disappointed, you can enjoy yourself on my behalf~|Commander, would you like me to apply some sunscreen to your skin? There's no need to be hesitant, I'm actually quite good at it~|Enterprise, South Dakota, it's all right to have a showdown, but don't drag others into it~
112011.feeling5: As your personal doctor, I will always be by your side, ready to– Hm? Doctors don't usually dress like this? Aha~ It's fine though, isn't it~? I want to go on a date with you, after all~
112011.unlock: Listen, everyone~! Playing by the beach is fun, but please keep safety in mind! If you begin to feel ill, come see me~!
112011.drop_descrip: Listen, everyone~! Playing by the beach is fun, but please keep safety in mind! If you begin to feel ill, come see me~!
112011.mission: Commander, I'm thinking about giving you the "Hygiene in Summer" mission~
112011.home: Commander, please don't forget to change clothes once we get back home. Otherwise, you may catch a cold from wearing wet clothes.
112011.expedition: I think those girls are starting to develop tans from going on so many commissions.

202270.detail: I really admire the head of the Royal Maid, Miss Belfast... She can do anything and has a strong will to boot... I hope I can become like her one day.
202270.touch: A fizzy drink? ...What am I going to do with you? I suppose you can have just one bottle, all right?
202270.login: Good morning, Commander. Did you sleep well?
202270.hp_warning: It seems I let my guard down...
202270.feeling2: Doesn't Dido worry a bit... too much? She works so hard, and I know you don't hate her, but... please, watch over her some more, Commander.
202270.mission_complete: This mission's reward is quite sizeable. Congratulations, Commander!
202270.main: It's not good to strain yourself by overworking. How about splashing some water on your face to refresh yourself?|It seems like the price for this ingredient has gone up... Commander, from now on, we'll have fewer dishes that use this.|Commander, watching you easily handle your work makes me feel happy... I wonder why?
202270.feeling5: Whew... I've finished cleaning the room. Next... Oh, welcome back. I'll prepare your meal right now, so please wait a moment, Commander.
202270.unlock: Good day. I am Hermione, from the Royal Maids. I'm delighted to make your acquaintance, Commander.
202270.feeling4: Commander, if it doesn't bother you, would you mind leaving your laundry to me? Washing our clothes together saves time, but more than that, I want you to personally feel how great your clothes feel after being hand-washed by the Royal Maids♪
202270.feeling1: Commander, why are you so stubborn...
202270.propose: You'd like for me to stay by your side, forever...? Of course, Commander. Taking care of you is my job, after all. Ah, would this be what's called a "confession"...? Yes, of course. Commander, I'll be in your care, from now, 'til the end of time.
202270.profile: I'm Hermione, a Dido-class ship belonging to the Royal Navy. In the past... I chased after Bismarck and participated in anti-submarine warfare in Sardegna... Besides that, there's nothing worth mentioning. Commander, do you have any questions?
202270.touch2: Commander, it's good to pay attention to the time and place when doing something like this, you know?
202270.mission: Commander, the more you don't deal with your work now, the more you'll have to deal with later.
202270.home: Commander. For the time being, you're forbidden from doing more work, okay? You need to make sure to take a break from now and then.
202270.win_mvp: I'm sure Commander will be elated~
202270.expedition: Commander, let's put our work on hold and go to greet the team that's just returned from commissions.
couple_encourage: Dido, it's not good to worry so much
Miss Belfast, please allow me to watch and learn!
202270.mail: Is this mail for you, Commander...? I apologize. I'll leave it here.
202270.feeling3: Commander, are you working overtime today? Then I'll bring over some coffee. ...Um, it's not a bother, you know? After all, being by your side no matter what is a Royal Maid's duty.

101173.detail: New Year... and Lunar New Year... are different? I don't really get it... Although, any day with good food and lots of sleep... is a good day. Mhm.
101173.touch: I totally don't feel like leaning against your shoulder, Commander. Nope, not at all...
101173.login: The Commander's still not back. I might just fall asleep here... Zzzzz...
101173.main: I'm wearing limited-edition Lunar New Year bunny ears and bunny slippers... do you like them? I like them.|I think Zed is interested in old Lunar New Year folklore...|Sitting on top of this tree makes me feel like I'm going to blossom, too...
101173.unlock: "Have a happy New Year. Let's pray for everyone's good luck"... Is that enough...? *Yawn*, I'm tired... Can I go home now and take a nap...?
101173.drop_descrip: "Have a happy New Year. Let's pray for everyone's good luck"... Is that enough...? *Yawn*, I'm tired... Can I go home now and take a nap...?
101173.touch2: Commander, are you having weird thoughts again...?
101173.home: You know the crackles and pops firecrackers make after you light the fuse... *Ughh*... Those are so noisy...

703011.detail: Commanding the fleet isn't your only job. You've also got to live up to everyone's expectations, and keep going no matter how tough things get. I'll be there to make sure you do.
703011.touch: I suppose now's a good time for a nap... *yawn*...
703011.login: Make yourself at home. I don't like being uptight all the time.
703011.main: Hipper and I surprisingly have much in common. I like talking about food and guitars with her.|Kirov has a thing for barging into my room and ask me to go drinking with her... Still, I'll take that over the antics of Gangut and the rest.|Care for a hot beer? If you want a little spice added to it, let me know.
703011.unlock: What, you've never seen the inside of a shipgirl's room? It's not like you're here on official business, so stop standing around already. Find a place to sit and relax.
703011.drop_descrip: What, you've never seen the inside of a shipgirl's room? It's not like you're here on official business, so stop standing around already. Find a place to sit and relax.
703011.home: Good work out there. Get some rest, you've earned it.

301812.detail: My bag is unzipped? Must be one of Foo's pranks. It's definitely not because Kasumi left in a hurry.
301812.touch: I dropped something? Thanks for telling me, Commander.
301812.login: You're right on time, Commander. Just like Foo and Kasumi.
301812.main: Foo follows Kasumi everywhere, to and from school, and even in class.|There are will-o'-the-wisps around port... Maybe Foo can befriend them.|I wish Foo could help me with my homework.
301812.unlock: Kasumi and Foo are excited about the new semester. Are you too, Commander?
301812.drop_descrip: Kasumi and Foo are excited about the new semester. Are you too, Commander?
301812.touch2: Commander, Foo is jabbing at you.
301812.home: You're giving a speech at the opening ceremony? I wonder what you'll talk about...

403053.detail: A ballroom dance...? Sorry, but I don't really know how to... I just need to follow your steps? O-okay, then I could... give it a try.
403053.touch: Commander, am I in time with your steps?
403053.login: So this is where you were. There are so many people in the hall, and I was worried about what I'd do if I'd lost you...
403053.battle: I will not let you disrupt the party for everyone else!
403053.main: Ajax... She's not planning something weird for the party, is she?|Everyone here is having so much fun... I could never even imagine my past self being at a place like this.|Commander, my friends are calling for me. Could you excuse me for a bit?
403053.feeling5: Thanks to all the friends I have now, I don't feel lonely anymore. And my encounter with you might be the happiest moment of my life. Ahahah~
403053.unlock: It's so fancy, so formal... Is this a "party"? I'm not sure I'll be able to fit in... But if you'll go with me, Commander, I'll give it a try!
403053.drop_descrip: It's so fancy, so formal... Is this a "party"? I'm not sure I'll be able to fit in... But if you'll go with me, Commander, I'll give it a try!
403053.touch2: Commander, people are staring at us.
403053.home: Not everyone in the Royal Navy is like Ajax. I can actually have a productive conversation with most of them...
403053.mail: I know the party is still going on, but you still have to check your new mail.

408081.detail: This hat is not a bulb of garlic, but a shark. A scary shaaaark. Raaawr.
408081.touch: Hm, this outfit is very cute, and U-110 likes it a lot. However, it makes me not scary. That makes me a cute shark. Raaaawr.
408081.login: Commander, let's go to school together?
408081.mission_complete: Commander, U-110 has defeated the homework. I'm strooong!
408081.main: U-110 learned from school that there are actually many kinds of Enigma machines... School is coooool. |Raaaawr, raaaawr, raaaawr! Amazon said I can't rawr at school, so U-110 will rawr when hanging out with Commander. |Bulldog says it's no fun to play with U-110, but she always plays with U-110 anyway. What a nice girl.
408081.unlock: Whenever I play games with Bulldog, I always end up losing. Frustratinggg. That's why... I'll study hard. One day, I'll winnnn.
408081.drop_descrip: Whenever I play games with Bulldog, I always end up losing. Frustratinggg. That's why... I'll study hard. One day, I'll winnnn.
408081.mission: The homework is strong... but U-110 is stronger. That's why I'll finish it all.
408081.home: Commander, why does everyone like flicking U-110's hair?
408081.mail: U-110 has learned a new codebreaking method. Want me to try it on the mail?

403052.detail: I'm so glad that I can finally practice cooking! I want to give something back to all the kindhearted people here!
403052.touch: Thanks to Juustagram, even people like me who aren't very sociable can still chat with everyone... Oh look, Graf Zeppelin just made a new post!
403052.login: Welcome back, Commander! Um... I heard from Ajax that you have a very "special" hobby... but what kind of hobby is it?
403052.battle: To protect everyone who has shown me so much kindness... I won't let you take a step closer!
403052.main: Ajax... You're not pulling my leg this time, are you?|Hipper is a totally different person on the internet compared to how she is in real life. Maybe she just has trouble expressing herself around people she cares about...|Miss Illustrious, could you teach me how to make tea? Admiral Hipper invited me to a tea party between the Royal Navy and Iron Blood, but I've never brewed tea before...
403052.unlock: I never dreamt that I'd be able to don this outfit and live a normal, peaceful life... Thank you, Commander...
403052.drop_descrip: I never dreamt that I'd be able to don this outfit and live a normal, peaceful life... Thank you, Commander...
403052.touch2: Commander, I want to give you a hug too~
403052.home: Welcome back! Cellphones are totally amazing, aren't they? No matter where we are, we can contact each other with the press of a button!
403052.win_mvp: Commander, can you take a picture to celebrate me getting MVP? I want to show it to my friends!
403052.mail: Prinz Eugen is surprisingly clumsy with this kind of stuff. She's still chicken-pecking with one finger.
403052.lose: I knew it... this totally reduces my fighting capabilities...

301014.drop_descrip: The whole world's going to feel the tremors from my debut! I'm Fubuki, the Special-type idol!

202271.detail: Commander... Even ships can get sick. Please, make sure to take care of yourself, alright?
202271.touch: Commander, let me perform an examination on you. Please come here and lie down on your side.
202271.login: Hm? Commander, what brings you back here...? Umm, are you here to be... inspected?
202271.main: Gosh, Commander... If you pretend to be sick, even I'm going to get mad at you!|Commander, don't you think this dress is a bit too small for me...? Um... I just feel like it doesn't fit me...|Commander, please make sure that you pay attention to your own health. After all, I can't attend to you around the clock.
202271.unlock: My, what brings you here, Commander? Are you feeling unwell? That's no good... Why don't you come sit over here first? I'll start by taking your temperature...
202271.drop_descrip: My, what brings you here, Commander? Are you feeling unwell? That's no good... Why don't you come sit over here first? I'll start by taking your temperature...
202271.home: Commander, please wait there for a moment. I'm examining someone else right now...

107381.detail: This shawl you gave me is really cozy. Hehe, let's huddle up like this... There, now we share the warmth.
107381.touch: Would you like to learn how to pin a specimen, Commander?
107381.login: Welcome back, Commander. Let's warm you up with a nice, hot drink. Would you like coffee or hot cocoa?
107381.main: If the opportunity presents itself, I might just host my own exhibit. Perhaps I could call it... "Caracal"?|I wouldn't mind sharing some of my prized specimens with you, Commander. You'd take good care of them, wouldn't you?|*click*! Nice, a fine new addition to my photo collection. I name it... "Fleet Commander, in Profile." Hehehe~
107381.feeling5: *yawn*... Oh, was I dozing off just now? Sorry for that, Commander. I just feel so relaxed when I'm with you... But thanks for lending me your shoulder to rest on. Hehehe~
107381.unlock: Commander, welcome to my "Utopia." Here, you can find my prized collection. Now, where should we start our detailed tour?
107381.drop_descrip: Commander, welcome to my "Utopia." Here, you can find my prized collection. Now, where should we start our detailed tour?
107381.touch2: Both specimens and girls alike must be treated delicately. Understood, Commander?
107381.home: Did you come across a new specimen I could add to my collection, Commander? Hehehe~

408080.detail: I'm not a garlic bulb, I'm a shaaaark. Fear meeee. Raaaawr.
408080.touch: Commander, I'll give you a swirly-whirly if you play with meeee.
408080.login: Commander, did you bring swirly-whirly candies?
408080.hp_warning: U-110's awesoooome. I'm not giving uuuuup.
408080.feeling2: You mean my Enigma machine doesn't have any use anymore? Okey-dokey, then let's play a game of decipheriiiing.
408080.mission_complete: Rawr! I've brought the mission rewaaaaards.
408080.main: Codebooks, codebooks... Oops, I forgot them in the dorm.|Commander, let's plaaaaay. Leeeeetttt'ssss plaaaaaayyyy.|I got lectured for pretending to be a shark... But I still had fun.
408080.feeling5: The Commander is my friend. I'll give you some of my codebooks. That way it'll be fine even if I forget mine. Yup-yup.
408080.unlock: Raaaawr. U-110 is a shaaaark. Fear meeee. Mess with me and I'll bite yooouuu.
408080.feeling4: Bulldog's really smart. Playing with her is fun. Next time, you should come play with us tooooo.
408080.feeling1: Why won't you play with me...
408080.propose: Commander is so nice to me. I love you. U-110's gonna bite anyone who messes with you. U-110's scaaaryyy. Raaaaaawr!
408080.drop_descrip: Iron Blood Type IXB submarine – U-110.
408080.profile: I'm U-110, Iron Blood Type IXB submarine, and I'm really good at commerce raiding. The Enigma machine I've got in my backpack is awesome. I'm awesome too, I just left my codebooks and charts behind...
408080.mission: Commander, once your mission's doooone, let's plaaaaay.
408080.home: Commander, your office is so booooring.
408080.win_mvp: Raaaawr. U-110 scared the enemies awaaaay.
408080.expedition: Commander, someone's come back to pooort.
408080.mail: I'll take care of your encrypted maaaail.
408080.feeling3: Believe it or not, this hairstyle was born with meeeee. Mhm, I'm a shaaaark. Raaaawr!
408080.lose: Codebooks, where are my codebooks... Goodie, they're safe...

408051.touch: Hey, Commander? No intimacy right now, okay? I'm fine-tuning this compound, you see...
408051.login: Now we add some of this, then– Whuah! Don't surprise me like that, Commander! You nearly just caused an accident!
408051.battle: Time for an experiment on you numskulls!
408051.main: Now we raise the heat slightly, then... Oh, God! I-it's on fire!|Experiments necessitate preciseness. Being even one 100th of a milliliter off affects the result!|The glamor of this lab coat drew me to the science room! ... Huh? This ISN'T a lab coat? Aha, ahahahaha...
408051.unlock: It's time for science class with U-73! Now, Commander, let's try out an exhilarating and positively fascinating experiment!
408051.drop_descrip: It's time for science class with U-73! Now, Commander, let's try out an exhilarating and positively fascinating experiment!
408051.touch2: You wanna be the target of my experimental fuel-powered torpedoes?

302070.detail: Sometimes, I feel like I'm not quite myself... That must be my other Self...
302070.touch: Did you need something from me?
302070.login: Commander, um... good job making your way over here.
302070.battle: I'd like to wait a bit more and see what the situation is like...
302070.hp_warning: We should get back into formation.
302070.feeling2: Commander, if there's nothing for me to do, I'll be heading to the shrine behind the mountain to help out.
302070.headtouch: Would you like to touch my horns?
302070.mission_complete: Oh, speaking of which... I haven't told you to receive the mission rewards yet... have I?
302070.main: Commander, if you're concerned that the tea is too hot... Um, should I blow on it for you?|Abukuma, I don't think that "only eating and sleeping" is a healthy lifestyle. I'm wrong about that? Well...|The destroyers are... well, they're always so full of energy and zipping about, that it's honestly a bit hard to keep pace with them...|Even when we can't see her, my Self is always by my side.|You want to know more about my Self? Do I think she has some kind of special connection with the meaning of my name...? I sometimes wonder myself.
302070.feeling5: Whenever I think of you, I always worry that something bad might have happened to you. Please, stay with my Self's... no, my side. That way, I won't have to worry.
302070.upgrade: Oh, I feel something awakening inside me...
302070.unlock: Um... Would you happen to know where the Commander might be? My name is Yura, and I have just arrived here today. Are you the Commander? Um, do you have a signed note or certificate that corroborates that?
302070.feeling4: Your fortune said that bad luck would follow you around, so I, along with Abukuma and the others, made a protective charm that will ward off evil. Please be careful, and always carry this around with you.
302070.feeling1: I wonder if the fortune that foretold "calamity" was referring to you...
302070.propose: Oh, to think that I'd be able to become your betrothed, Commander. ...Is this truly alright? Hehe, I'm so happy that I lost my composure... Thank you.
302070.drop_descrip: Nagara-class light cruiser number four – Yura.
302070.profile: I am the Nagara-class light cruiser, Yura. In a certain great war, I was the flagship of the Fourth Torpedo Squadron for a short period of time. I might have taken my leave earlier than my sister ships in that war, but this time, I swear that my Self will remain until the bitter end.
302070.touch2: I have no choice but to become your wife now, Commander. Hehe~
302070.mission: Oh, Commander, I really think you shouldn't be neglecting these missions...
302070.home: It's good to see you, welcome back. I apologize, for I don't really know where to put these papers...
302070.win_mvp: My Self played a big role as well. I'll have to thank her for her help.
302070.expedition: The girls are back from commissions. If you require assistance, shall my Self accompany you?
couple_encourage: Well... Let's try to stay safe.
My friend? Mm, I'm not sure what you mean...
Can you see my Self?
302070.mail: Shall my Self read it aloud for you?
302070.feeling3: You want to know more about my Self? Well, she's also a part of me... Mm, if I were to put it simply, she's kind of like my familiar.
302070.lose: It might be better to withdraw first...

308021.detail: School's just boring compared to the ocean... Like, there's tons of undiscovered fish species and monsters down at the bottom of the ocean! I wish I could see how they look~
308021.touch: You should give this anglerfish plushie a hug! It's really soft and cuddly!
308021.login: Innsmouth! ... Hehe~ Did I spook you, Commander? Don't worry, this is just a stuffed toy!
308021.main: Big fish eat regular fish. Regular fish eat small fish. Hang on... what do small fish eat, again...?|If you were an anglerfish, you could work late at night without having to turn on the lights!|It's not easy to swim without a swimsuit~ Baww...
308021.unlock: Many secrets lie at the bottom of the ocean! Commander, let's go looking for them next time! It'll be like a field trip~ Heheh!
308021.drop_descrip: Many secrets lie at the bottom of the ocean! Commander, let's go looking for them next time! It'll be like a field trip~ Heheh!
308021.touch2: Haven't I told you I'm not a fish?!
308021.home: We've finally got recess, and yet you still go on sorties... Great work~!

202039.touch: Are you unable to endure that much? Yes yes, lie down over there... Hmm? You want to be stepped on... is that what you're trying to say?
202039.main: What? You want me to step on you that badly?|When I see you, Commander, I yearn to abuse you. Perhaps this is a form of love|nil
202039.unlock: I'm in a good mood today, so I'm giving you special permission to lick my feet. Come on, show sincere thanks to my reward!
202039.drop_descrip: I'll allow you to lick my feet since I'm in such a good mood today. What? I can't believe you'd turn down such a great opportunity!
202039.touch2: Commander, are you looking for punishment again? Tonight I'll make you feel like you are in heaven and hell at the same time!

408050.detail: Now, now, Commander, don't stress over everything~ I'm sure it'll all go fine.
408050.touch: What is it? Got something I could help with? C'mon, tell me something.
408050.login: Howdy-do, Commander! Welcome back! I'm all good to go and ready to sortie! Just give me the order.
408050.battle: The leader of wolfpacks, that's me!
408050.hp_warning: Mein Leben! Better perform emergency maneuvers...
408050.feeling2: Oh? Finally managed to catch a break, Commander? Then let's go for a quick stroll, shall we?
408050.mission_complete: With my support, we could finish these missions with our eyes closed!
408050.main: When you're underwater all day, sometimes you just wanna resurface and smash through the waves! ... Hey, Commander, wanna go for a quick dive in the ocean?|I'd rather be diving in the ocean and feeling the thrill of being near the enemy than stuck at port staring into space all day...|Isn't it fun to hear what's on somebody's mind and help them with it? ... Maybe I ought to open a psychiatric booth. Anyway, Reichspfennig for your thoughts, Commander?
408050.feeling5: True, I can't guarantee I'll be speedy when I dive... but no matter what, you'll be mine, Commander! Especially your heart! Hahah!
408050.upgrade: Now my shots will be even more on point! Heh heh~
408050.unlock: U-73 of the Iron Blood, reporting for duty! If there's anything that needs doing, just leave it to me!
408050.feeling4: I suppose you've fallen for me at last? Then stay by my side forever, Commander!
408050.feeling1: Uh... My friends are waiting for me, so sorry, gotta scamper.
408050.propose: Ahah, I didn't think this would happen so fast, but now you're a part of me! Relax, just let me handle everything for you! I'll take care of you for the rest of your life~
408050.drop_descrip: Iron Blood Type VIIB submarine – U-73.
408050.profile: I'm U-73, the Iron Blood submarine that completed lots of missions and served as the leader of several wolfpacks!
408050.touch2: Uh-huh. So, Commander, how many gut-punch torpedoes do you want for dessert?
408050.mission: So, we've got a mission. Let's do it together, Commander!
408050.home: Good to see you! Let me handle things for you while you get some rest~
408050.win_mvp: Heheh! Did you see how strong I am?
couple_encourage: U-boats, it's our time to shine!
408050.mail: Mail's just arrived~ Oh, do you want me to read it on your behalf?
408050.feeling3: The wild U-73 approaches quietly, waiting for her chance, and then POUNCES! ... Hahaha, I caught you, Commander!
408050.lose: Oh nooo...! Ahaha... How the heck could we lose...

112010.detail: Commander, I'm leaving the resupply of medical drugs and equipment to you
112010.touch: Wh-why is my heart beating faster...
112010.login: I, Vestal, am always ready to heal wounded people
112010.battle: I'm very happy to have become everyone's repair ship
112010.hp_warning: Oh no! I have to treat the injuries!
112010.feeling2: That reminds me. Commander, have you been paying attention to your health? I'm in charge of it? I don't mind, but please take care of it yourself, alright?
112010.main: Commander, if you keep daydreaming, I'll leave you alone and go play with Enterprise!|Commander, have you checked your fleet's condition before sending them out?|Has Enterprise been eating properly? I'm really worried...
112010.feeling5: This is what a personal doctor is like...! 24-7 full-time care, and taking care of your well being! --Eh? That's too much? Is that so...
112010.upgrade: It's so good that I can take better care of everyone now~
112010.unlock: Greetings, Commander. I am repair ship Vestal. I worked exclusively for Enterprise. I'm happy if everyone is healthy~
112010.feeling4: Hmm...  As a guardian angel, I have to treat everyone equally, so I can't just take care of you, Commander. However, personally speaking, I cannot say I can't provide you some extra~ spe~cial~ ser~vice~
112010.feeling1: Commander, as punishment for angering me, this injection will be painful
112010.propose: Hahaha, now you'll never be able to reject my nursing, Commander~ What are you getting embarrassed for~ It's alright to leave everything to me, you know?
112010.drop_descrip: Repair ship ー Vestal, Hull Number AR-4!
112010.skill: Yeah yeah, it's time for repairs~
112010.profile: I am the one in charge of maintenance, Vestal. I was tasked to look after Enterprise exclusively, so if there's anything up, please say the word. But if you underestimate me just because I'm a 'support', you'll have another thing coming, you know?
112010.mission: Commander... um... I think we should check the missions one more time...
112010.home: Commander, please tell me if you are hurt
112010.win_mvp: Don't worry. With me, the fighting damages can be repaired.
112010.expedition: The girls of the commission team have returned. I wonder if they got injured...
couple_encourage: Enterprise, don't be so rash!
Big sis is here. It's gonna be fine!
Don't get hurt, my little monkeys!
112010.feeling3: Yes, yes~ It seems you're too reliant on me recently~ Well, I'm happy that I'm so trusted, but Commander, you might become totally useless at this rate...
112010.lose: I will not abandon everyone. Let's all return together.

403054.detail: My sister's always pushing this "for the glory of Iron Blood" stuff onto me. Can't she do this idol stuff herself...?
403054.touch: These hands are no longer weapons of war, but for returning the admiration of my fans. Right, I can do this...!
403054.login: Commander, do you mind if I practice here?
403054.battle: We're not done with the lesson yet...
403054.main: Um... Maybe it's because I'm so used to working with everyone, but I feel like it's actually pretty easy being onstage.|Commander, do you think you can stop my sister from getting everyone to hold up those "World's♡Cutest" signs when I go on? It's really embarrassing...|Idols are there to make people smile... I never thought I could do something like that.
403054.feeling5: There was a time when I wanted nothing more than to break these claws off my hand. But now, I feel pretty good about all this "idol" stuff... Commander, I never thought it could ever live like this. Hehe.
403054.unlock: My sister just wouldn't stop bugging me, so I finally caved and agreed to do this... Anyways, all I have to do is get up on stage and sing, right?
403054.drop_descrip: My sister just wouldn't stop bugging me, so I finally caved and agreed to do this... Anyways, all I have to do is get up on stage and sing, right?
403054.touch2: Commander, have you forgotten what my hands can do?
403054.home: "Commander, you did so well...! Commander, keep at it...!" That should be idolish enough, right?
403054.win_mvp: Commander, can we go home now?
403054.mail: Commander, I got a new offer. Should I take it?
403054.lose: Have we been spending too much time on idol lessons...?

103020.detail: Sometimes good things happen when you're just coasting across the sea.
103020.touch: Oh, it's you, Commander. I thought it was Pensacola...
103020.login: Commander, want to go swimming together?
103020.battle: Those aren't allies up ahead. Ready all weapons!
103020.feeling2: Helena, could you go find something interesting with that radar of yours? Wait... that's San Diego? Great, let's go play in the water together!
103020.headtouch: Your hand feels just like Pensacola's...
103020.mission_complete: Can we go join the party now?
103020.main: If you don't know how to swim then I can teach you, Commander.|Shell Kiska Island? Ahaha... that'd be a new experience for me.|Enterprise is too strict. Please don't be like her, Commander.
103020.feeling5: Welcome back, Commander! I was just about to finish drying your laundry. I cleaned up the books and other stuff that was lying around. How's it look? The tidiest it's ever been, right? And dinner will be... Hm? Why am I doing all this? Well, you know... just preparing for what comes later!
103020.upgrade: Us pretty girls need to take care to maintain our good looks.
103020.unlock: Commander, I'm Salt Lake City, a heavy cruiser! You think I'm exposing too much? Well, I gotta keep a close eye on my waist, you know?
103020.feeling4: You can always rest on my lap if you get tired, Commander. Don't worry, I won't play any tricks on you. ... Hm? I've always been this kind to you!
103020.feeling1: Commander, that look in your eyes kinda creeps me out...
103020.propose: It's a promise, Commander! Every day from now on you'll hang out with me and do the stuff I enjoy. Like surfing, beach volleyball, and... scuba diving, I guess? Of course, I'll hang out with you and do all the stuff you enjoy, too~!
103020.drop_descrip: Pensacola-class Heavy Cruiser – Salt Lake City, Hull Number CA-25!
103020.skill: The best defense is a good offense!
103020.profile: I'm Salt Lake City, second ship of the Pensacola-class. That's right, I'm a genuine heavy cruiser. My armor's thin because of that treaty thing, but my firepower holds up. Although, I participated in lots of battles in the Pacific and survived to the end of it, so maybe armor isn't that important. The battle of Attu Island? Luck is a power of sorts too, you know? ... No, no, I'm not arguing. Anyway, do you really want me to wear as much as Laffey does?
103020.touch2: Hey, don't do the same stuff Pensacola does...
103020.mission: Who cares about missions, let's party!
103020.home: Oh man, my skin is on fire... Sorry, Vestal, think I could ask for a spa treatment from you?
103020.win_mvp: This time it wasn't just all luck!
103020.expedition: Whew, those girls went out on a commission in this blazing heat? They even completed it, too. Must be awful out there~
103020.mail: New mail for you. Oh my, is this a love letter? ... Hmm... Okay, now where's the trashcan?
103020.feeling3: Commander, don't you ever get bored of lying around on the beach? Why don't we play some beach volleyball? Sun burn? No worries, Pensacola has already rubbed me down with sunscreen.
103020.lose: Wuah! I'm out of armor-piercing shells... damn!

202272.detail: Actually... I bought this swimsuit back when it was on sale. I'm relieved that you like it...
202272.touch: Wow, the sea is so pretty~ ...Hmm? I'm even prettier than the sea...? Jeez, Commander... Don't get all sappy on me now.
202272.login: Commander, please leave work at the office, and relax to your heart's content today.
202272.main: These waves feel so nice~ Why don't you dip your feet in too, Commander? ...Hm? A big wave is... Eek!|Overexposure to the sun isn't good for your skin. Why don't we move somewhere else in a little bit?|A nap? Y-yes! Please take your time and relax to your heart's content. If something happens, hm... don't worry, I'll make sure you wake up when that happens.
202272.unlock: Commander, I've brought the chair. If you don't want to get in the water, feel free to sit here. ...Hm, me? Of course, I will remain by your side.
202272.drop_descrip: Commander, I've brought the chair. If you don't want to get in the water, feel free to sit here. ...Hm, me? Of course, I will remain by your side.
202272.home: I've prepared a cool, refreshing drink for you. Please enjoy.

405011.detail: Apologies, Commander. Am I acting differently from usual? At times, I don't even know which is the real me...
405011.touch: A dance...? Oh, no, I wouldn't turn one down, I just haven't been asked until now...
405011.login: How's your work coming along, Commander?
405011.mission_complete: A decoration for the banquet? Splendid work.
405011.main: Commander, would you invite Tirpitz for me? Apologies, I'm... still not sure how to ask her myself. |I can keep a lot of people satisfied merely by sitting here with a smile... but only because of my status as the fleet leader of the Iron Blood. |As a leader, I must sometimes say and do things that I do not believe in. Commander, I hope you never lose sight of who you are.
405011.feeling5: In front of my compatriots, I always had to be adamant, solemnly spearheading the march of the Iron Blood. To be the leader of the Iron Blood's indomitable fleet, I had to lock away the Bismarck that struggled to express herself... But when I'm with you, Commander, I can set aside that burden, just for a little bit...
405011.unlock: My sincerest apologies for the delay, Commander. Ah, excuse me... as the fleet leader of the Iron Blood, I'm expected to wear this outfit to various formal occasions. Just putting it on seems to make me inadvertently change the way I speak...
405011.drop_descrip: My sincerest apologies for the delay, Commander. Ah, excuse me... as the fleet leader of the Iron Blood, I'm expected to wear this outfit to various formal occasions. Just putting it on seems to make me inadvertently change the way I speak...
405011.touch2: C-Commander... don't tease me like that...
405011.mission: Having unfinished work will turn even the finest wine into vinegar. Isn't that right, Commander?
405011.home: Let us raise our glasses to the heroes who have returned from battle.
405011.expedition: Once the commission fleet has finished dropping off their supplies, let's invite them to the banquet as well.
405011.mail: Even at the most lavish banquet, it is your responsibility as commander to be well-informed should the situation change.

101174.detail: So like, I go like this? And then I say the line? Uh... "such biiig thankieees~, siiir~" was that it? Feels like Javelin's shtick.
101174.touch: Smile? ...like this? I don't get it...
101174.login: Welcome, Comma– valued guest. That was close. Almost messed it up....
101174.main: I fell asleep and Z23 yelled at me... Z23 sucks...|This job is really hard... but spending time with everyone isn't so bad...|I'm working so hard, there's no way I can fail... but I am kinda sleepy. What should I do...?
101174.feeling5: Turns out working sucks way more than I ever imagined, but... seeing the Commander's face in a whole new light like this... makes me happy.
101174.unlock: I'm done changing... how is it? Today, I’m supposed to call you "valued guest?" Um... I don’t really get it...
101174.drop_descrip: I'm done changing... how is it? Today, I’m supposed to call you "valued guest?" Um... I don’t really get it...
101174.touch2: Commander, are you a perverted customer?

103090.detail: Being stared at like this... is really embarrassing...
103090.touch: I'm not used to this whole "physical contact" thing, but if it's a request from the Commander, then...
103090.login: Commander, is there something I can help with...?
103090.battle: I've been assigned a task, so I have to do my best!
103090.feeling2: Do you need me for something? I'm currently helping the others carry some supplies.
103090.mission_complete: Yay, the mission rewards are here~! *Hngh*...! *Pant*... Commander? I can't lift these by myself, can you come lend a hand?
103090.main: Commander, this is r-really... e-embarrassing... |Um, sorry... I'm not really sure how to turn people down... Besides, isn't it good to make others happy...? |I'll have you know that I've turned down plenty of requests before! For example... uhh... umm, I can't think of any right now...
103090.feeling5: Commander, when I'm with you, I can only think of how much I want to do something for you, how much I want to help you, and how much I want to become your strength...
103090.upgrade: Hopefully I've gotten a tiny bit stronger...
103090.unlock: C-Commander... Pleased to meet you... I'm the New Orleans-class heavy cruiser, Quincy. Um, since we're going to be living together from now on, is there anything I can help you with?
103090.feeling4: Why do I like helping others so much? Well, it's because we can only build a brighter future if we all work together.
103090.feeling1: Even if you're this kind of person, I won't give up on trying to help you! Probably...
103090.propose: Eh? You'd like me to always stay by your side? Um, actually... I want to rely on you, and be relied upon. I want to understand what you're thinking, and I want to... be with you forever... *Whimper*... This is embarrassing...
103090.drop_descrip: New Orleans-class heavy cruiser – Quincy, hull number CA-39.
103090.skill: Why must we hurt each other...
103090.profile: I am Quincy, the New Orleans-class heavy cruiser. I'm not fond of fighting... It'd be better if everyone could help each other out...
103090.touch2: C-commander... e-even I can get mad!
103090.mission: Commander, we have new missions. I'll help you out as well.
103090.home: Good work today, Commander. Welcome back!
103090.expedition: The commission fleet is back. Should I help bring the supplies in? Okay, leave it to me!
103090.mail: Commander, I've finished arranging the mail.
103090.feeling3: Hurting others is more painful than being hurt yourself... Huh? Doesn't everyone feel that way?
103090.lose: *Ugh*... Is this the best I could do?

299031.detail: Don't think I didn't notice you earlier, Owner! You left to play with someone while I wasn't looking, didn't you? Not that I mind, really! But you could've at least let me known first!
299031.touch: Need to lie down, Owner? Okey-dokey! Which headrest do you want: my thighs, or my soft tummy? Hehehe♡
299031.login: Are you feeling good, Owner? Yay, then it's time to start our seaside date!
299031.main: There's only one reclining chair? So what~ We'll just share it, silly Owner~ I'm pawsitively fine with doing it that way♡|I'm all thirsty! Time to chuggy-chug a nice, cool drink! ...Mmhh! I feel like a new person!|Fishing? Nuh-uh, I don't wanna. Time spent fishing could be time spent playing games with you, Owner!
299031.unlock: Cheer up, Owner! Jeez, why are you so bummed out when we're at the beach... Because it's just a normal playdate instead of a romantic date? What's the difference anyway? C'mon, let's go head down to where the others are~!
299031.drop_descrip: Cheer up, Owner! Jeez, why are you so bummed out when we're at the beach... Because it's just a normal playdate instead of a romantic date? What's the difference anyway? C'mon, let's go head down to where the others are~!
299031.home: Wow, there are so many cuties here besides me! But, heheh, I'm the top cat when it comes to being cute and sexy! Isn't that right, Owner?

405010.detail: Is there something on my face?
405010.login: I look forward to working with you.
405010.battle: Follow me, not Eugen. Come – we shall face our opponents, no matter how numerous they may be!
405010.feeling2: I am not so easily impressed.
405010.mission_complete: I'm leaving the mission rewards over here...
405010.main: Is there a problem? Perhaps my combat experience could prove useful? |"Operation Rheinübung?" I don't have fond memories of it... |Such a slovenly expression, Commander. Now! Lift your chin, puff out your chest, and let me see those eyes! Hut!
405010.feeling5: I... know that I'm not the best with words, but.. I want you to know that... I enjoy being at your side...
405010.unlock: Guten Tag, I am Bismarck. I have fought many foes on many fronts. You may call upon me whenever there is a problem.
405010.feeling4: Why are you staring at me? Do I have something on my face? I'm pretty, you say...? Um, thank you...
405010.propose: ... Commander, what kind of expression should I have at a time like this? I should... just smile?
405010.skill: Truth can only be found within our range!
405010.profile: I am the Iron Blood battleship entrusted with the name Bismarck. Allow me to prove that Iron Blood engineering is the finest in the world, no matter the battlefield. Eager to see for yourself?
405010.touch2: I... am not good at expressing myself. Please do not tease me on purpose...
405010.mission: Those who cannot finish their missions have no right to stand on the battleground.
405010.home: You've done well. You've earned your rest.
405010.win_mvp: Such honors may please a weakling, but I am strong.
405010.expedition: ... The commission team has returned. I'll go greet them first.
couple_encourage: Tirpitz... forgive me...
Eugen, don't go overboard with your games.
No one can stop the march of the Iron Blood.
405010.mail: Be diligent about checking your mail.
405010.feeling3: You're not a bad commander... What? Is it so strange for me to give compliments? ... You're simply overreacting.
405010.lose: For tarnishing my pride... next time, you will pay with your lives.

105200.detail: Commander, I'm hungry. Think you could get me a roast turkey?
105200.touch: You're interested in my abs? Go ahead and feel 'em.
105200.login: Oh, it's you, Commander. I almost mistook you for a shady person and sent you flyin'.
105200.battle: I won't let y'all leave until I've had my fun!
105200.hp_warning: Well well, aren't you the frisky bunch... Ahaha!
105200.feeling2: Commander, can you call Tirpitz out here? I've always wanted to see which one of us is stronger, but she always ignores me.
105200.mission_complete: Commander, I'll go fetch the mission rewards. I'm big and strong, after all!
105200.main: Commander. Com-man-der. Commanderrrr~ Oh, I didn't need anythin'. Just felt like callin' for you. |I'd like to have a Turkey Shoot. Makes me wish I could fly... |Sure is nice outside. Commander, wanna go lie in the grass under the sun? I could stay like that all day...
105200.feeling5: Commander, can you come to my room tonight? Um, I've always hugged a stuffed animal to help me sleep, but I was thinkin'... maybe you'd be even better...
105200.upgrade: I feel like I could beat someone up right now... Mmh!
105200.unlock: I'm Alabama. You need somethin'? ... Prepare for duty? Oh, sure. Got nothin' better to do, so might as well. Let's go!
105200.feeling4: Commander, let me give you a hug... This feels really nice and puts my mind at ease. Mhm, I like it.
105200.propose: Is this a promise to become my personal hugging' pillow? Will you let me cling to you as I fall asleep every night? Mm... that makes me happy. Commander, can I start huggin' you now?
105200.drop_descrip: South Dakota-class battleship – Alabama, Hull Number BB-60.
105200.skill: Don't die on me just yet!
105200.profile: I'm Alabama, fourth ship of the South Dakota-class, also known as Lucky A... What else? Uhh... I received some honors while fighting in Norway, the Marshall Islands, and the Marianas. Then, there was Leyte and the trip to the Sakura Empire... Since then, I've just been taking it easy in the Mobile Bay.
105200.touch2: Huh......? Commander, the hell are you doing?
105200.mission: Commander, what's this big ol' stack of papers? Oh, I see... so those are the missions...
105200.home: Commander, come sit in my lap. Huh? Isn't everyone doing this nowadays?
105200.win_mvp: Kickin' the enemy's ass is all in a day's work for me. What are you praisin' me for?
105200.expedition: I can see the commission fleet comin' back over the horizon. Mhm, I'm real proud of my eyesight!
couple_encourage: Sis, I'll be the one to beat them to a pulp, okay?
I challenge you, Tirpitz!
105200.mail: What's up, Commander? Oh, the mail? Ah, um, I forgot to bring it over. Give me a sec.
105200.feeling3: I've been gettin' along pretty well with the Sakura Empire girls. I thought they'd hold a grudge against me, but turns out that wasn't the case at all. Mhm, they're an interestin' bunch!

301010.detail: Hehe, are you that lonely Commander?~
301010.touch: Help with work? O right… Looking at the Commander being so idle, I almost forgot about work~
301010.login: Commander, how are ya feeling today?~
301010.battle: Good weather, even better mood~ Let’s go!
301010.hp_warning: Looks like this isn’t the time to joke around...
301010.feeling2: What’s in my hands? I think it’s called “Gohei” or something like that. It looks so pretty when swung back and forth, so I thought to grab it with me~
301010.mission_complete: Commander, the mission rewards are here~ With me being here, perhaps there are more rewards now? Hehe.
301010.main: The weather today sure is beautiful, don’t you think, Commander? |Listen up {namecode:14}, even if the Commander is a total loser, but I am totally (probably) reliable! |Even if the Commander praises 100 times, that still won’t be too much... hmm, or perhaps 100 praises will be a bit tiresome to listen to.
301010.feeling5: I was implying something before? Regardless, no matter what type of girls you like, as long as you will like me in the future, then that’ll be just fine~ Hehehe.
301010.unlock: Yoohoo~ yours truly {namecode:2} class has arrived, so you’re the Commander? I'm looking forward to your guidance~
301010.feeling4: What type of girls do you like, Commander? Hmm? I’m just curious. Ha~ perhaps you’ve misunderstood me?
301010.feeling1: I thought the Commander would understand me...
301010.propose: Even though I said that the Commander would like me “in the future”, but it seems that “future” has become unexpectedly sooner~ Were you a bit shy when I asked you?~ Hehehe.
301010.skill: Hmph, taste the power of the Special type Destroyers!
301010.profile: Yoohoo~ I am the destroyer who recently made the world tremble, call me {namecode:2}! Sorry, I’m not trying to be complacent, in fact, I was in many battles… although none of them are worth writing home about… I will continue to do better!
301010.touch2: Wow! You scared me to death!
301010.mission: Commander, there are so many uncleared missions—— ahhh~!!! Were you being lazy again?
301010.home: First, you do this, then this....?! C-Commander, welcome back~ Hahaha, I wasn’t up to anything!
301010.expedition: Hey~ The Commission fleet is back, stop sleeping!
couple_encourage: Let’s give the enemy a taste of our might!
301010.mail: Here’s some mail~ ah… So it’s for the Commander...
301010.feeling3: Not sure how my sisters are faring… Although, since they are my sisters, I’m sure they’re prospering wherever they are!
301010.lose: That hurts so much… Commander, let’s run away!

299032.detail: Welcome, welcome, Owner~ If you've got any requests, don't be shy, don't hesitate, I'll try my best and sing a song that's really great~♡
299032.touch: Is there something I can do for you, Owner?
299032.login: Owneeeeeer! ...Oopsies, that was improper of me! I'm dressed like a refined Dragon Empery lady, so I need to act the part!
299032.mission_complete: Mission complete! Let's claim those rewards right meow, Owner~
299032.main: My beloved Owner~♡ Squeeze, cuddle, sniiiiff~ I love being with you so much~♡|Sexy cleavage, trendy fashion, and obligatory kitty ears: the perfect package of cuteness~ How do you like it, Owner?|Relax and get cozy, Owner~ Now's not the time for work, it's time to hang out with me!
299032.unlock: I'll sing a song for you, Owner~ Ahem... Wait, I'm not sure I know any Dragon Empery songs, actually...
