299032.drop_descrip: Welcome, welcome, Owner~ If you've got any requests, don't be shy, don't hesitate, I'll try my best and sing a song that's really great~♡
299032.touch2: I'm always okay with getting intimate with you, Owner~
299032.home: Hey Owner, what do you think of everyone's dresses? Are there any outfits you want to see me in? ...I look gorgeous in my current one? Squeeee! I love you, Owneeeeer~♡
299032.expedition: The girls just came back from that commission! I wonder if Drake was with them?

308030.detail: I love the serenity of the night. Nobody ever notices my presence.
308030.touch: It's important to warm up before diving. Commander, let's do some exercises together.
308030.login: Commander, submarines will die if you take them out of the water. I-I was just kidding...
308030.battle: I'll let the rest of you handle the anti-sub.
308030.feeling2: Now that we're all on the same team, I'm going to have to learn to work with Indianapolis... but that sister of hers, bleh... Ugh, maybe I'll just go for a swim instead...
308030.mission_complete: These mission rewards... there's nothing that can be brought underwater...
308030.main: It's not like I'll die if I'm taken out of the ocean, but I definitely prefer being in it. *blub blub* |Commander, when it comes to swimming, which stroke is your favorite? Crawl? Butterfly? Breaststroke? |There are a lot of miraculous things in the ocean. Want to go on a dive with me and experience it for yourself?
308030.feeling5: It's hard to let go of the past... but Commander, you've rewritten everyone's futures, to one where we can all move forward together. Commander, I can't be prouder of the fact that I fell for you.
308030.unlock: I-58, reporting in. I usually like hanging out in the water by the docks, so you know where to look if you need me~
308030.feeling4: Although we can't become close friends that easily, at least we're making some progress... I suppose time will take care of the rest. Commander, thank you so much for your help. As a reward... *kiss*
308030.feeling1: Does this fleet exist only to wage war...?
308030.propose: Commander, I'm sure that you will be able to create that world... where everyone can smile from the bottom of their heart... As for me, I can't think of anything happier than being with you right now.
308030.skill: Can you predict where I'm going to attack from?
308030.profile: Type-B Mod 2 cruiser submarine, I-58. Yup, that's me. I was born towards the end of the war, and participated in several missions. Before the end of things, I managed to sink Indianapolis. Even though it was a great achievement, it's not like it ultimately made a difference...
308030.touch2: I mean... I'll admit they're on the small side... but that makes it more hydrodynamic!
308030.mission: New missions? Is there something that I can do?
308030.home: Commander, are the conditions of the waters suitable for me to carry out my activities?
308030.win_mvp: Is that all you surface-lubbers are made of?
308030.expedition: I wonder what's going on up there on the surface... Ah, Commander, your commission fleet has returned.
308030.mail: Commander, there's new mail... Ah, sorry, I just left the water so I got it wet...
308030.feeling3: "A journey of a thousand miles begins with a single step?" Hmm... I suppose I can start by saying hello to her...
308030.lose: I've been found, huh... Next time, I've got to be sneakier...

304050.detail: Don't let anyone get injured? Commander, that's quite the tall order, but I'm up for the challenge.
304050.touch: Ehehe... Oh, Commander, I was just thinking about what snacks I'd like to eat.
304050.login: Commander, I've left today's combat operation plans on the table. Please take a look.
304050.battle: All right, let's proceed as planned.
304050.hp_warning: Perhaps a change of plans is in order...
304050.feeling2: Information is a tactician's most valuable asset. Knowing more than your enemy is already half the battle.
304050.mission_complete: Mission rewards... we should think of the most efficient way to utilize them.
304050.main: The road ahead of us is perilous, but I believe that is also what makes the journey worthwhile. |Commander, there is no need to fear failure. As long as I am here, all setbacks are but fodder for our victories. |Akagi turned out... a bit differently from what I expected.
304050.feeling5: Commander, if you truly care about me, *cough* then please keep moving forward with all your might. Your gallant victories and smiling face are the best medicine for me.
304050.upgrade: My health... seems to have improved a bit.
304050.unlock: *cough* *cough* Battlecruiser Amagi, reporting in. It looks like I should be able to fully utilize my abilities here. Commander, would you please brief me on our enemies?
304050.feeling4: *cough* *cough*... Commander, you've already earned my acknowledgment. Why not have a little more confidence in yourself?
304050.feeling1: Swineherds like you are quite hard to find these days.
304050.propose: Commander... so you've chosen me, then? Hehe... From the beginning, I was prepared to lay my life down for your ambitions. But with this being the case, perhaps I should take better care of my body.
304050.drop_descrip: 1st Ship of the Amagi-class Battlecruisers, Amagi
304050.profile: I am the nameship of the Amagi-class battlecruisers, Amagi. Along with Akagi, I was originally supposed to be converted into an aircraft carrier, but that plan was scrapped after a certain natural disaster. *cough* *cough* ... As you can see, my body is not in a great condition, but please do not worry about me too much.
304050.touch2: Oh, Commander... I was contemplating some other things...
304050.home: Commander, were you able to make use of my strategic plans?
304050.win_mvp: Now then, how can we make further use of this victory?
304050.expedition: Commander, a commission has been completed. Also, I have some suggestions for potential candidates to send on the next-
couple_encourage: Akagi...? Oh my, I have the wrong person...
Akagi, follow the commander's orders, okay?
304050.mail: Commander, you have new mail. Might it be new intel?
304050.feeling3: Superior tactics can only make up for differences in strength to a limited extent... *cough* *cough* ...That is why becoming stronger is still of paramount importance, Commander.

301329.detail: This one's for Kisaragi... this one's for the Comainder... this one's for me... Okay, that's everything!
301329.touch: Comainder, you want candy, too? Here!
301329.login: Comainder, what candy do you want today? I have all kinds!
301329.main: Co-main-der! Comain-der! Comainder! Hehehe~ I just wanted to say your name!|What candy do you like, Comainder? I'll bring more of it next time!|Comainder, let's call Kisaragi over so we can play house together!
301329.unlock: Comainder, I'm done retrofitting! Have some candy! Hm? You're always nice to me, so I'm giving you some candy!
301329.drop_descrip: Comainder, I'm done retrofitting! Have some candy! Hm? You're always nice to me, so I'm giving you some candy!

301011.detail: I didn't oversleep! I was just doing stuff I like and ended up losing track of time...
301011.touch: Commander, you got any more work you need help with? I've gotta go walk the doggy in 15 minutes!
301011.battle: Let's finish this so I can make it to school!
301011.main: nil|The Fencing Club, the Reading Society, the Economics Association, the UFO Research Organization... Dang it, I wanna join them all!|Belfast's going to hang out with Edinburgh after school... Maaan, I wish my sisters would come see me, too...
301011.unlock: Oh no! I-I'm gonna be late for school! Y-you need to speed up too, doggy! *Pant*... *pant*... Why'd none of my sisters wake me up before they left?!
301011.drop_descrip: Oh no! I-I'm gonna be late for school! Y-you need to speed up too, doggy! *Pant*... *pant*... Why'd none of my sisters wake me up before they left?!
301011.lose: Fight or run away to fight another day!

301570.detail: Hyaa! C-Commander, when did you get here?
301570.touch: Commander? Would you like to try the sakura mochi that I made?
301570.battle: My s-skirt is gonna get blown away!
301570.hp_warning: O gods, please give me guidance...!
301570.feeling2: Back then, my sisters and I were all scattered to the winds... But, we are finally reunited again. It's a miracle...
301570.main: O gods, please bless this port so that everyone may come home safely. |Yoizuki may seem cold, but she's very nice and is always thinking of everyone else! |Good luck! I'll... be supporting you!
301570.feeling5: C-Commander, please accept this! This is a protective good luck charm! "Marriage tie?" What do you mean...? C-Commander... you're a big bully...
301570.upgrade: C-Can I truly become stronger like this?
301570.unlock: I was guided here by the gods... Ah! M-My name is Harutsuki! Pleased to meet you!
301570.feeling4: Y-You'd like to watch my kagura dance? B-but, I still have a lot of practicing to do... Fusou said that rehearsals are just as important as practice...? I see! I... I'll do my best!
301570.feeling1: Commander, I wonder if you've been cursed...
301570.propose: O gods, thank you very much for allowing me to meet Commander. I truly am blessed right now! So, um, Commander... though I'm still inexperienced, please take care of me!
301570.skill: O gods, please watch over us!
301570.profile: I am the ninth ship of the Akizuki-class destroyers, Harutsuki. Due to various circumstances, I wasn't able to do much, but... I'll make up for it this time, Commander!
301570.mission: C-Commander, umm... there are still missions left...
301570.home: Commander, you're safe! Thank goodness... my prayers were heard...
301570.win_mvp: Surely this must have been the gods' blessings.
301570.expedition: Commander! E-Everyone has come home safely!
301570.feeling3: Aww.... m-my hair's all messed... Fusou's not here either, what should I do... Hm? You'd help me comb my hair? Thank you very much, Commander!

102098.detail: Anything I worry about? Nothing at all. ...Actually, I shouldn't keep things secret from you! Not that I could even if I wanted to. Hahahah!
102098.touch: I've never cuddled with someone like this before... It might take some getting used to, but I still like it. Hehehe~
102098.login: I was just thinking you'd be back soon, and here you are! Maybe we share a telepathic link through our hearts! Hehehe~♪
102098.battle: This time, I fight for the commander!
102098.main: Anything you wanna do, or anything on your mind? You can tell me anything♪|How happy you make me feel? Hmm, I feel as happy as the ocean feels big, I guess? Hehehe~|You're worried about people meddling with us? Hehe, there's no point worrying about that stuff when we have each other!
102098.feeling5: To think I'd ever get to put on these clothes and spend my joyful time with the person I love... (Hug) I guess being a girl really is pretty sweet. Hehehe~
102098.unlock: Man, this is so embarrassing... C-Commander, w-w-what do you, umm, like, think of my d-d-d-dress...?
102098.drop_descrip: Man, this is so embarrassing... C-Commander, w-w-what do you, umm, like, think of my d-d-d-dress...?
102098.touch2: N-no probs! I'm ready for this! So just go ahead and, umm, y-you know...
102098.home: Okay, just leave everything to me! I know just how much force to put into my grip to make you feel good!
102098.mail: Here's your mail. Give it a look later.

301322.detail: Chocolate bananas and taiyaki~ are all delicious~ but compared to candy...? Let's call it a draw~
301322.touch: Aww... my scooper broke again... goldfish scooping is so hard! Comainder, come help!
301322.main: The fireworks are so pretty~ Comainder, can we put on fireworks every day? |Comainder, I want this candy! Um, I want that one too! |The prize for goldfish scooping is a special flavor candy?! Comainder, let's go do that right now!
301322.unlock: Comainder, I put on my yukata just like you said! Ehehe, you should take me to the festival so I can get lots and lots of candy!
301322.drop_descrip: Comainder, I put on my yukata just like you said! Ehehe, you should take me to the festival so I can get lots and lots of candy!
301322.touch2: The candy's going to fall out!
301322.home: Ahh! If we don't hurry to the festival, all the candy will be gone!

301012.detail: I-I feel my consciousness... flapping away...
301012.touch: C-Commander, don't touch me... I'm going to lose my balance...
301012.login: C-come on in! ... Oops, I mean, welcome back, Commander!
301012.battle: It's so hot... Let's mop up the enemies quickly so we can go home...
301012.main: I did promise Akashi I'd be the mascot... but it kind of feels like she tricked me...|Could you help me pick these up, Commander? Wearing this makes them... mmrgh... impossible to reach, you see...|What? The forecast warned about high temperatures? ... That's no biggie, I've already gotten used to it being really hot...
301012.unlock: "C-come on in! We've got special offers for you!" ... W-wait, is this really what a "sexy mascot" would wear? It feels pretty different from what I was expecting... And boy, is it stuffy in this thing...
301012.drop_descrip: "C-come on in! We've got special offers for you!" ... W-wait, is this really what a "sexy mascot" would wear? It feels pretty different from what I was expecting... And boy, is it stuffy in this thing...
301012.touch2: Wh-what? What the heck are you doing, Commander?
301012.win_mvp: Heheh! Wearing this costume... doesn't impact my performance at aaaall!

301819.detail: Kasumi is here, so Foo is never lonely. And Kasumi has lots of friends, so everything is good.
301819.touch: Foo said, "I wish I could talk to the commander too."
301819.login: Hello. Foo and Kasumi have been waiting for you.
301819.main: Kasumi wants to help people. Foo does, too. We're gonna try to be as helpful as we can.|Kasumi has more energy than before. If you feel tired, just sit next to Kasumi and rest.|Shiranui became a friend, so Foo isn't scared of her anymore.
301819.unlock: Kasumi thinks that her outfit has gotten a bit breezier. Foo said the same thing.
301819.drop_descrip: Kasumi thinks that her outfit has gotten a bit breezier. Foo said the same thing.
301819.home: Welcome back, Commander. Kasumi brewed some tea. Have a cup.

301571.drop_descrip: Happy New Year, Commander! I am currently on my way to give a Kagura dance at the shrine. If you have time... would you like to come see it?

301323.drop_descrip: I heard that if I go around telling people "Happy New Year," I can get lots of goodies! Ehehe, I hope they'll give me a bunch of candy!

103091.detail: I'll just stay here and help watch everyone's belongings. Uh... I'm really not very good with exercise...
103091.main: It feels like... everyone is staring at me when I wear a swimsuit... It's so embarrassing... |Beverages? Don't worry, I came prepared. |Listening to the sounds of the sea really puts me at ease...
103091.unlock: Everyone's so cheerful and energetic... Commander, um, if you're tired, want to rest here with me?
103091.drop_descrip: Everyone's so cheerful and energetic... Commander, um, if you're tired, want to rest here with me?
103091.touch2: *Whimper*... Could you please not do stuff like this in front of everyone...?
103091.home: Would you like to have some cold drinks? Be careful not to have too many at once, or you might get a brain freeze~

301820.detail: I love the way countless flowers bloom vividly during the spring, but even so, I wouldn't want it to be spring all year long - that would be unfair to the flowers that only bloom in other seasons. Mhm, I'm sure the four seasons exist so that all flowers have a chance to bloom. Hehe~
301820.touch: Anything you need me to do, as long as it is within my abilities, I would gladly do for you.
301820.login: Welcome back, Commander. Shall we continue our work? Should you have any concerns, please feel free to consult me. I shall do all I can to assist you.
301820.battle: Be careful, everyone. Watch out for the submarines...!
301820.hp_warning: Ngh... As long as the others are safe...
301820.feeling2: The sun is shining brightly, and it's another beautiful day outside. Commander, if you aren't busy, would you like to view the flowers with me?
301820.mission_complete: Congratulations! As expected Commander, you've completed our missions with flying colors!
301820.main: Commander, do you prefer herbal tea, or black tea? |Commander, Harutsuki seems to have gotten herself in some trouble. I'd like to check on her, so would you mind if I left you for a bit? |"The sun in the west, the moon in the east, canola blossoms inbetween." I'd love to see this scenery myself.
301820.feeling5: Commander, I hope this is not too presumptuous of me, but may I decorate your office with some fresh flowers? I want to give you something that reminds you of me, even when I am absent... It's just a little selfish whim of mine, hehe~
301820.upgrade: I see, I see. That was quite educational.
301820.unlock: I, destroyer Hanazuki from the Sakura Empire, would like to extend my humble greetings to you. As a member of the Akizuki class, I specialize in anti-air and anti-sub warfare, but please do not hesitate to call upon me where I am needed.
301820.feeling4: Some flowers bloom all year long while others are fleeting and ephemeral. Some are purely ornamental, while others have therapeutic uses... Commander, do you like flowers that bloom dazzlingly, or those that bloom silently and out of view? ...Ah, sorry, I'm not making any sense...
301820.feeling1: Commander, I do not wish to see you ostracized by anyone... But at this rate, I may not be able to do anything for you...
301820.propose: I see that while my heart was still wavering, you've already made up yours. Then, I won't hesitate to reciprocate your feelings either... Hanazuki will gladly accept this ring. I'm so glad that I can be someone who is important to you...
301820.skill: Hanazuki is here to offer support!
301820.profile: I entered service during the tail end of the War as an Akizuki-class specialized for anti-air and anti-submarine capabilities... Err, I guess it was the Fuyutsuki-class... Or was it the Michitsuki-class... Err... S-sorry, I still have a lot to learn, so I'd greatly appreciate your guidance!
301820.touch2: Eek?! Um, if I may be so bold... this sort of behavior is... It would be best not to do this to the other girls...
301820.mission: So many unfinished tasks... Commander, wh-where should we start?
301820.win_mvp: It's only right that I offer my gratitude to everyone who fought alongside me.
301820.expedition: The commission fleet has returned. Commander, should I bring some herbal tea with me to welcome them back?
couple_encourage: Anti-sub, anti-air patrol, be careful!
How does your garden fare today?
301820.mail: New mail seems to have arrived. If you need me to sort it for you, please let me know.
301820.feeling3: It's embarrassing to admit it, but... I tried to pick up gardening several times but kept getting stuck because I couldn't decide what I wanted to grow... Commander, do you have any flowers that you're partial towards? I want to make up my mind this time!
301820.lose: I see, because of my indecisiveness... I am terribly sorry for dragging everyone down...

202290.detail: Hmm... You're staring at me so much... Did you happen to want these gloves?
202290.touch: ...Hm? Is something amiss? I do believe I've been doing everything to your specifications...
202290.login: Commander, are you going on a sortie? I shall stay here and await your return.
202290.feeling2: I shall wait for you here tomorrow as well, just as you instructed, Commander.
202290.headtouch: Nnh... Are you treating me like a child?
202290.mission_complete: "Remind the commander to collect the rewards for completed missions." ...Got it. Commander, please remember to collect your rewards. What rewards? Umm...
202290.main: Paperwork, paperwork... Where did I put it again? On that shelf? I can't seem to remember...|Pepperpot? ...Why yes, I do think that food generally tastes better with a healthy pinch of pepper.|I want to get along with U-410. ...Mm, with you here, Commander, I'm sure it will be fine.
202290.feeling5: No matter how much time passes, I will continue to wait for you here, Commander. No matter what, I'll always wait for you to come back.
202290.upgrade: Have I become stronger than before?
202290.unlock: Arethusa-class light cruiser... Penelope, is my name. From now on, I will be your subordinate. I hope that you... can at least remember my name.
202290.feeling4: Would you like some of the rosehip tea that Aurora taught me to make? ...It's too sour? Hmm... Maybe I accidentally added vinegar...
202290.feeling1: Commander... aren't you acting a bit weird?
202290.propose: A promise ring... proof that you always want to stay with me? Mm... But, even without this, as long as you think of me, sometimes call for me, and look at me... that's all I need.
202290.profile: I am Penelope of the Royal Navy, Arethusa-class light cruiser. I participated in a transport mission with Aurora and her companions in the K Fleet. There were difficult times, but I managed to pull through. If only I had noticed her back then...
202290.touch2: Hm...? Commander, what are you doing?
202290.mission: "Remind the commander if there are any unfinished missions." ...Got it. Commander, you have unfinished missions. What are they about? Umm...
202290.home: I am glad that you have returned safely, Commander.
202290.win_mvp: Commander, I followed your instructions and emerged victorious.
202290.expedition: The commission has been completed, and now I'm supposed to welcome the fleet back... But what comes after that?
couple_encourage: I'm counting on you.
Aurora, we're together again.
Neptune... Um, sorry...
Did you say something...?
202290.mail: Hmm... Ah, I knew I was forgetting something... Um... Right. The mail. Commander, I brought you the mail.
202290.feeling3: If I leave the uncompleted work here, I wonder if eventually, I won't have to do it anymore.
202290.lose: I have been defeated. My sincerest apologies...

108040.detail: I wonder if there's a way to become friends with Yuubari, that girl cooped up in the science department...
108040.touch: You want a fight with me? You asked for it! Take *this*! Blue knockout punch!
108040.login: Welcome back, Commander! Let's part these curtains, like... This! Hehe, now the sun's gleam reaches in here too!
108040.feeling2: Bluegills are, in fact, a type of sunfish! ...You knew that? Welp, and here I was hoping to tell you a surprising fact.
108040.mission_complete: Mission complete! Now it's time for a swim! ...Huh? Too early for a swim? But why?
108040.main: Sunny days are always good swimming days!|Hey, that's not a blank sheet, that's Bluegill's personal file on the back! Look! I wrote the whole thing myself!|How long are you gonna have a staredown with your desk, Commander? C'mon, let's catch a break!
108040.feeling5: So my hugs really put you in a pickle, huh, Commander... I'm sorry for that! I can't help it, I just feel super, *super* happy when I hug you! Hey, what if I wait with my hugs until you say you're ready? Okey-dokey! Just tell me whenever you want one!
108040.upgrade: Wooo! Wow, I've really gotten nimbler!
108040.unlock: I've finally found one! My own commander! ...Hehehe, from now on, you're Bluegill's commander!
108040.feeling4: I figured out why my hugs bother you! It's because it feels embarrassing, right? Well, don't worry about that! I asked around, and nobody thinks less of you for it! ...W-was I wrong?
108040.feeling1: It's okay! You just need to bask in the sunshine for a bit, and your troubles will surely all go away!
108040.propose: Can I hug you now, Commander?! Yay! Sharing a hug with you just feels like total bliss~ Hehehe~ Stay put, I wanna enjoy our embrace a little longer!
108040.drop_descrip: Gato-class submarine – Bluegill, Hull Number SS-242.
108040.profile: I'm Bluegill, Gato-class submarine. I saw action all over the sea and gave my enemies a real scare. Hehe, I'll shine on at this port, too!
108040.touch2: Whoa, whoa! Commander! You've kinda crossed a line here!
108040.mission: Commander, if you're heading out for a patrol, why not take Bluegill with you? It might be good to have me!
108040.win_mvp: I hereby name this victory "The Battle of Bluegill"!
108040.expedition: Commander, the rewards from that commission have arrived!
couple_encourage: Whoa, is that a new piece of gear?!
Gato-class, let's go!
108040.mail: Is this mail for Bluegill? Oh, it's addressed to the Commander...
108040.feeling3: There you are, Commander! Come here! ...What's wrong with me hugging you? Am I holding you too tight? That's not it? Then what is it?
108040.lose: They nearly got us... But it won't go the same way next time!

301270.detail: Your Grace... Please don't stare at me so...
301270.battle: Naught but death awaits those who oppose my master.
301270.feeling2: A true ninja has no need of emotion. She needs only her master's will to execute.
301270.mission_complete: Your Grace, mission rewards have been issued. Inspect them at your leisure.
301270.main: Hm...? Your Grace? Did you want me to say something?|I am not sure what to say... But I would be happy to listen to anything Your Grace wishes to impart.|The flower in my hair? It was a gift from Oyashio. Oyashio, she's... very colorful.
301270.feeling5: So this is an "emotion"... before such things I had no problem keeping a clear head, but even now it seems not so wicked... Yes, this "emotion" drives a powerful need to stand by Your Grace's side, and it grows ever stronger.
301270.upgrade: I stand ready to execute your will.
301270.unlock: Third ship of the Kagerou-class, Kuroshio reporting in... I am here to carry out my master's will.
301270.feeling4: Your Grace, I beg your pardon. Recently I find myself distracted from the mission, thinking again and again about Your Grace's "communication." Please, you must punish me...
301270.propose: I once thought that absolute devotion to the mission was all there was to being a ninja, but I have learned so much from you, Commander... I, Kuroshio, from this point forward, am no longer your shadow alone, Commander, I am now your partner. And we will stand together until the end of our days.
301270.profile: Third ship of the Kagerou-class, Kuroshio. As part of the 2nd Fleet and Destroyer Division 15, I joined in the Battle of the Java Sea, operations in the South Pacific, the Third Battle of the Solomon Islands, and other engagements until I was sunk during a transport mission. ... I will not let that happen again. I will commit all of my resources to ensure that I am of service to Your Grace.
301270.touch2: As this body belongs to Your Grace, please do with it as you will... Nnng... Aaaah...
301270.mission: Your Grace, a new mission has been issued.
301270.home: Your Grace, are you tired? Is there any way I can be of assistance to you?
301270.win_mvp: I am Your Grace's shadow. I have no need of glory or acclaim.
301270.expedition: Your Grace, the fleet you dispatched on commission has returned as scheduled.
couple_encourage: For the master...!
301270.mail: Your Grace, a letter has arrived.
301270.feeling3: While I struggle with Your Grace's concepts of "communication" and "games," still... I... can't say I dislike them.
301270.lose: Your Grace, it is time to retreat. I will cover your withdrawal.

301821.detail: Even though it's the same sea as always, watching the clouds with you while wearing this unusual outfit is filling me with novel sensations I've never felt before...
301821.touch: Do you need me to lend you a swim ring?
301821.login: Today may be my day off, but if there is anything I can do for you, please do not hesitate to call upon me.
301821.main: Look, Commander, that coral reef... Hehehe, the "flowers" in the sea are quite beautiful as well, aren't they? |This swimsuit... took a lot of agonizing over, but I eventually made my decision... Commander, what do you think? Does it look good on me? |Gah...! ...Ah, s-sorry! I was just looking at the ocean... and suddenly shifted into anti-submarine mode... I know I shouldn't be so uptight during time off!
301821.unlock: I've heard some say that summer is the season of cherry blossoms, lotus petals, and sunflowers, but... If you ask me, being able to leisurely enjoy the breeze with you feels pretty good too. Hehe~
301821.drop_descrip: I've heard some say that summer is the season of cherry blossoms, lotus petals, and sunflowers, but... If you ask me, being able to leisurely enjoy the breeze with you feels pretty good too. Hehe~
301821.touch2: Eek?! Ehh?! S-sorry! Ah, um, Commander, the strap is...
301821.home: Are you weary, Commander? If so, why not try some of my lavender honey tea? It's great for recovering from fatigue.

403031.detail: Woah! I got a pretty dark tan after playing with Wales all day...
403031.touch: Commander, have you seen Wales? That rascal, she ditched me again!
403031.login: Commander, I am practicing my smile. Someone said it looks unnatural, but what do you think?
403031.main: Wales, someone is going to break your hand again if you keep messing with Bismarck! I won't plead for you this time...|Despite her devil-may-care attitude, Wales is actually quite reliable. In fact, she helps me all the time, even though we were once enemies...|I went and told Hipper about our beach day, and all she said was, 'Why do I need to be jealous about your thin, lewd, and non-combat-ready swimming suit?' Haha, that's so like her!
403031.unlock: Relaxing on a float, gently licking my lips... is this really the most popular photo pose for the beach? Wales, you’re not teasing me again, are you?
403031.drop_descrip: Relaxing on a float, gently licking my lips... is this really the most popular photo pose for the beach? Wales, you’re not teasing me again, are you?
403031.touch2: There are a lot of good things about Wales, but please avoid picking up her bad habits.
403031.mail: More mail? Any from Hipper or Bismarck? Ah, they're all for you, Commander... How boring...

10700030.detail: You want to come into my room? Hey, don't just casually walk in when I haven't even given you permission!
10700030.touch: Can I help you? Don't just stare blankly, answer me!
10700030.login: Good morning... Wait, what's with that pathetic look on your face? There's no way you're still half-asleep, right?
10700030.battle: Are these guys even worthy of being my opponent?
10700030.hp_warning: This is nothing I can't handle!
10700030.feeling2: I'm thirsty... Huh, this orange juice is for me? And it's 100% orange juice to boot! You've got sense!
10700030.headtouch: Eek! ...Hey, can you not touch me out of the blue?!
10700030.mission_complete: You're finally done. Though, considering the amount, it's only to be expected.
10700030.main: This office isn't bad at all. Still, when compared to my room, it needs work.|"Manjuus" refers to those round birdies at the port, it seems. I thought everyone was referring to the snack.|Do you really think you have time to rest? Can't you see the mountain of work piled up in front of you?
10700030.feeling5: The view from here is so gorgeous... Eek! You! Say something if you're there! ...Well, it's fine. Why don't you come sit here and enjoy the view as well?
10700030.upgrade: That's pretty good. I guess I can thank you for this.
10700030.unlock: Hello, hello~! My name is Iori Minase! It's such a pleasure to meet you! ...Huh? There's no need for me to force myself...? Hey, wait a second, what do you mean by that?!
10700030.feeling4: I wonder what I can do to shine more brilliantly on stage...? Sing harder? Make the performance flashier? ...Right, since you're here anyway, I'd like to hear what you think.
10700030.feeling1: Oh. So you were here all along?
10700030.propose: You've come to understand me quite well, haven't you. If you take your eyes off of my brilliant presence in the future, I'll never forgive you!
10700030.drop_descrip: Hello, hello~! My name is Iori Minase! It's such a pleasure to meet you! ...Huh? There's no need for me to force myself...? Hey, wait a second, what do you mean by that?!
10700030.skill: Make sure you keep your eyes on me!
10700030.profile: My name is Iori Minase! My goal? Of course it's becoming a top idol♪ You should feel honored every second you're in the presence of the super idol, Iori! Heehee♪
10700030.touch2: Eek! ...Where do you think you're touching!
10700030.mission: You still have work left to do? Hurry up and get it done!
10700030.home: Oh, you're back? Perfect timing, it's time for you to accompany for tea time!
10700030.win_mvp: How naive of you to think that you'd be a match for me!
10700030.expedition: Oh, it looks like they're back from commissions. I suppose I can go greet them in person.
couple_encourage: Ami, stop playing around! Let's go!
This much is nothing! Heehee♪
Azusa, let's go!
10700030.mail: There's some mail for you. Since I've gone out of my way to let you know, go and check it ASAP!
10700030.feeling3: I have a close friend who's been with me all the way since my childhood. Isn't that right, Bunny-bun?
10700030.lose: I, Iori Minase... lost? I'll take some more lessons, and I swear I won't lose next time!

403030.touch: Have you finished having your fun?
403030.login: Hmm~ What is it? How would you like me to train you today?
403030.feeling2: ... I don't smile enough? Commander... care to see if you can make me?
403030.mission_complete: Commander, the rewards. My portion? Not interested~
403030.main: If you overwork yourself too much... you ~ will ~ die.|Lucky ship? Are you mocking me?|Operation Rheinübung? Looking back, that was how it all began for me.
403030.feeling5: ... Why did I laugh? Because it's funny to see you look so confused, Commander... This smile is truly from the bottom of my heart!
403030.unlock: Hmm... so you're the Commander? How long can you keep me amused? I'm looking forward to it.
403030.feeling4: Ich liebe dich~ is this a joke or the truth? Why don't you decide for yourself~
403030.feeling1: Mind getting out of my sight? You're a bit of an eyesore.
403030.propose: So this is the answer you're giving me? What shall I do? What a dense commander. I have long stopped being the empty person I was before. Did you forget that you were the one who changed me?
403030.drop_descrip: Admiral Hipper-class Heavy Cruiser, Prinz Eugen
403030.skill: It's not enough. I. Want. MORE!
403030.profile: I am Prinz Eugen, the miracle of the Third Reich and the third ship of the Admiral Hipper-class heavy cruisers. I will survive any battle, no matter how fierce. Luck? You sure have some guts.
403030.touch2: Now then, it's my turn to have a taste of you.
403030.mission: Missions... aren't there any interesting ones?
403030.home: Commander, won't you shower and relax with me for a while?
403030.expedition: Commission completed? Let's see if there is anything interesting to report.
couple_encourage: You Eagle reporters sure do run fast!
Is it a tradition for you all to be so flat?
Let's see how long you can keep up that "elegance"...
Chicken Squad? Whatever, I'll play along...
403030.feeling3: Commander~ I love you. Just kidding. Did your heart skip a beat?

301830.detail: I give off warm and fuzzy vibes? Ehehe, I've heard that from the others as well~ It's a little embarrassing... Nuh uh, I don't mind at all. I'm really glad to hear it!
301830.touch: I'm more than just a ball of fluff, you know? Look, it's my smile and my ability to bring warmth to others that counts~
301830.login: Welcome back, Commander! Um, Naganami will always be waiting for you right here! That's because, well... I'm happiest when I'm by your side!
301830.battle: I'm the flagship? All right, just leave it to me!
301830.hp_warning: My friends are still fighting, so I can't afford to go down here!
301830.feeling2: Everyone in the Mutsuki class is super fluffy and cute! Being at this port makes me so happy~!
301830.mission_complete: Mission complete! Great work today! Come, come, don't be shy – come rest on this big fluffy pillow!
301830.main: Jintsuu is always so knowledgeable and reliable... I wish I could be just like her... |Commander, can you let me be flagship next time? I'll work even harder, for the sake of everyone's happiness! |Lately, everyone has been circulating rumors that hugging me or cuddling my tail has healing properties, like coming out of a bath. They're even saying that it can cure colds... There's no way that's true, right?!
301830.feeling5: Still not enough good fortune in your life? ...You leave me no other choice then! Even if you have bad luck, there's a way to compensate for it! I just have to pass it to you directly... Mmwah~
301830.upgrade: The feeling of warmth and safety... this is what it feels like to get stronger... Commander, thank you very much!
301830.unlock: So this place is the port? Huh... Oh, Commander! I'm the fourth ship of the Yuugumo class, Naganami. It's a pleasure to finally meet you! Um... what's my selling point... Love! I love you, and everyone else as well!
301830.feeling4: Oyashio taught me a little trick! If I remember properly, it goes a little like... this! This circle on your forehead is supposed to make you luckier when it comes to your love life, and also helps you become happier!
301830.feeling1: Commander, if there's anything bothering you, please let me know. I'll be waiting for you... as long as it takes...
301830.propose: Um... Commander, I thought we had grown a lot closer, but this still feels a bit awkward... Wh-what should I do? ...Ah! Commander, try hugging my tail! I'm sure its warmth and fluffiness will help you loosen up! Mhm!
301830.skill: Try this torpedo strike on for size!
301830.profile: I'm Naganami, fourth ship of the Yuugumo class. During the War, I was primarily involved in transport operations, but I did participate in some large-scale operations and even served as flagship. Any hardship on the battlefield can be overcome as long as you believe in one another... I just know it!
301830.mission: I can probably help out with transport missions, but as for other tasks... By the way, Commander, I see you tackling all sorts of different missions every day! That's really amazing!
301830.home: Commander, good job in battle! Hurry, come sit over here~ I'm going to give your shoulders a nice rub!
301830.win_mvp: I didn't even realize I got MVP... But, this was only possible because of everyone's hard work!
301830.expedition: Commander, everyone in the commission fleet has come home. I'm sure they're all tired, so I'll go give them a warm hug!
couple_encourage: When we work together, the 2nd Torpedo Squadron will never lose!
It's an honor to fight at your side!
301830.mail: Commander, new mail has arrived. Here, I brought it for you. Maybe someone brought good tidings!
301830.feeling3: My tail is warm and fluffy, but Wakaba's is shinier in comparison... Hatsushimo's is slender, and Shimakaze's is tiny... Um, there are all different sorts!
301830.lose: I'll have to work much harder if I want to become an ideal flagship...

10700010.detail: You want to get to know me? Uhh, sure... To start with, what do you want to talk about?
10700010.touch: Do you need something, Commander? Oh! I'm guessing you need a hand with something.
10700010.login: Good morning, Commander! Let's roll up our sleeves and get to work!
10700010.battle: All righty, time to get fired up!
10700010.hp_warning: The show is far from over!
10700010.feeling2: I've loved singing since I was a kid. I especially love singing together with a group of friends!
10700010.headtouch: You like how my ribbon looks? Hehehe~ Thank you! It's my signature accessory!
10700010.mission_complete: Job completed! Way to go, Commander!
10700010.main: What were those little kitty creatures called again? "Meowfficers"? I bet our resident animal lover, Hibiki, would love to meet one!|I'm glad to see fellow idols at the port! They're all so cute, and so pretty to boot... I hope one day we can all go up on stage together.|I've played a villain character before, and I actually really got into the role! Didn't think it would be so fun!
10700010.feeling5: Commander! I made some cookies today! They came out pretty good, I'd say. Listen, I was hoping you could... have a taste and tell me what you think?
10700010.upgrade: I'll try to be the best, brightest-shining idol I can!
10700010.unlock: Hello, Commander! I'm the idol, Haruka Amami! I'll do my best to share my dreams with everyone in port! Let's all have a great time together!
10700010.feeling4: That's enough rehearsing for one day, I think... Are you taking a break too, Commander? Then we could sit and relax together! What do you say?
10700010.feeling1: Oops, sorry, I was busy reading the script. What were you saying?
10700010.propose: It's thanks to you and all the wonderful people here that I've managed to get this far and work with a smile. I want to bring a smile to your faces, just as you have for me!
10700010.drop_descrip: Hello, Commander! I'm the idol, Haruka Amami! I'll do my best to share my dreams with everyone in port! Let's all have a great time together!
10700010.skill: Here's a smile for all my fans!
10700010.profile: I'm Haruka Amami! I've loved singing ever since I was little, and always dreamed of becoming an idol. It's a tough job, but I know I can overcome any challenge as long as I have my friends! Hehehe~
10700010.mission: There's still a few tasks we need to do. If you need my help with any of them, just say the word!
10700010.home: Welcome back, Commander! I made snacks while you were out. Do you want some while you take a break?
10700010.expedition: Well done on that errand, everyone! Glad to see you made it back in one piece!
couple_encourage: Let's put on a top-notch show for the fans, Chihaya!
Thanks for that tip you gave me, Ritsuko!
Don't be silly, Ami, I'm not gonna trip on– Whuaahh!
10700010.mail: I think there's mail for you, Commander! Maybe it's a new job offer?
10700010.feeling3: Ow, oww... Oh, hi, Commander. It's nothing serious, I just tripped in the corridor... A bandaid? Aww, thank you so much!
10700010.lose: Urgh... Sorry for tripping up... I'll work on it so we win next time!

10700070.detail: You want to know more about me~? If you play with me, I'll show~ it~ all~!
10700070.touch: Oh, Commander! If you're free, come play with me~!
10700070.login: Commander, are you still asleep? If you don't get up soon, I'm gonna doodle all over your face~
10700070.battle: I wonder what kind of prank I should pull~
10700070.hp_warning: This is the part where I show off my true power...
10700070.feeling2: Oh, Commander! Have you seen Ami around? Hmm. We had promised to eat pudding together though...
10700070.headtouch: What is it? Do you want to play games with me, Commander?
10700070.mission_complete: Yay! We're done, Commander~! Now, let's go back and play games together!
10700070.main: There are so many people at the port that I can show my pose off to! If I train like this, I'll be able to become sexier in no time♪|Hey Commander, are you dozing off? Heh, I guess I'll use this opportunity to put some 'special' pictures on their desk...|Hiya Commander! Hm? What am I doing with this package? Hehehe~ Expect great things☆
10700070.feeling5: Gotta be careful so I don't wake them up... quietly... Woah, you were awake? ...I-I'm not playing a prank on you, I was just trying to drape a blanket over you! Believe me, Commander!
10700070.upgrade: Don'tcha think I leveled up my mature allure stat~?
10700070.unlock: Nihihi~♪ I'm the idol, Mami Futami! You'll get to feast your eyes on how alluring Mami is, so look forward to it, Commander~!
10700070.feeling4: I saw a really tasty pudding at the store earlier~! Oh, I sure want to eat some with the Commander~ ...Huh, you're going to buy some? That's the Commander for ya♪
10700070.feeling1: Wowow, even though I had the Commander pull for me, I didn't get a single Rare character!
10700070.propose: Commander! I'm so very terri-bully thankful that you always play with me~! The mature, alluring Mami, will continue to work hard in the future, so please look forward to it~♪
10700070.drop_descrip: Nihihi~♪ I'm the idol, Mami Futami! You'll get to feast your eyes on how alluring Mami is, so look forward to it, Commander~!
10700070.profile: The name's Mami Futami. Ami's my twin. When we do our hair the same way, we look exactly alike~! You think I'm actually Ami and not Mami? Ehehe~ Who knows~♪
10700070.touch2: Commander, has my mature allure made you fall head over hells for me~?
10700070.mission: Commander... let's finish work quickly and get it over with, yeah?
10700070.home: Welcome back, Commander! Hey hey, isn't it snack time yet~?
10700070.win_mvp: Yay, I won~! Let's see, what are the drops this time around~?
10700070.expedition: Good job returning safely! To the victor go the spoils!
couple_encourage: Let's get this party started!
Uh-oh, h-how about we work together for now, Ricchan~?
That's our Iorin for ya~♪
10700070.mail: Looks like there's a letter for you? I wonder if it's a love letter from someone~
10700070.feeling3: Save me, Commander! I got caught pulling a prank, and now I'm getting chased around! Let me hide over here for a bit~!
10700070.lose: Uegh! This wasn't in the job description~! Hurry up and retreat!

102231.detail: A bicycle must be maintained regularly, so I asked U-47 for advice and help. One day I need to offer her a favor in return.
102231.touch: Bicycling is an excellent way to train the body. Prepare your bicycle and we can go for a ride, Commander.
102231.login: Is it time to sortie? Please wait. I must park my ride somewhere first.
102231.main: It seems the academy has no bicycling club... Perhaps I should petition to create one... Hmm...|A new dessert shop opened, and their specialty is ice cream...? ... C-Commander, do you mind if I leave for a moment?|U-47, how about we go on a bicycling trip the next time you're off duty?
102231.unlock: Good morning, Commander. Unfortunately, this bicycle only seats one person, but I could dismount and lead it along as we walk together.
102231.drop_descrip: Good morning, Commander. Unfortunately, this bicycle only seats one person, but I could dismount and lead it along as we walk together.

101300.detail: I-is there anything we can do together, Commander...?
101300.touch: C-Commander, would you like to... um... have lunch together sometime?
101300.login: D-do remember the secret word? ... P-phew... Then it's really you, Commander...
101300.battle: Now is not the time for me to be scared... L-let's give them a beating!
101300.feeling2: I'm a bit of a scaredy cat... and I'm always afraid to tell people what I really think...
101300.mission_complete: Commander, I-I think you still have a few rewards you haven't collected yet.
101300.main: There are actually some obvious differences between us Fletcher sisters.|M-my heart beats so quickly... whenever I'm in front of you, Commander...|It really is a wonder... that all of us who ended up spread across the world could reunite here...
101300.feeling5: C-Commander, I want to tell you something... U-um, if you hold me in your arms, then I could say it... C-could you do that for me?
101300.upgrade: If only I was a little more brave...
101300.unlock: Y-you're the commander?... Hello, I'm Jenkins, a Fletcher-class destroyer... U-um, could you take me back with you?
101300.feeling4: How about we have some tea together after lunch... N-n-not like a date or anything like that...!
101300.feeling1: U-um... Please stop staring at me...!
101300.propose: You want to be with me forever and ever? As long as you're okay with it... then of course I'll be with you! D-do you... f-feel the same, Commander?
101300.drop_descrip: Fletcher-class destroyer - Jenkins, Hull Number DD-447!
101300.skill: I-if you don't run away now then I'll have to get serious!
101300.profile: I-I'm Jenkins, DD-447, one of the earliest Fletcher-class ships built. Truth be told, I'm actually not good at combat at all... I barely helped out at Kula Gulf or Kolombangara... Anyways... That's my story~!
101300.touch2: C-Commander?! U-um, I-I-I don't believe you should be doing this...
101300.mission: Commander, I-I think you still have a few unfinished missions.
101300.home: Good work, Commander. Is there anything I can help you with? Huh? There isn't...?
101300.win_mvp: Whew... I was so nervous I thought my heart was going to burst... H-hooray for victory!
101300.expedition: That supply fleet... Isn't the enemy this time around, right...?
101300.mail: Commander, you've got new mail. Would you like me to check it for you?
101300.feeling3: C-Commander... I'm feeling a little troubled...
101300.lose: *Pant*... *Pant*... T-the enemy hasn't caught up yet, have they?!

403033.detail: Hehe... Commander, that's quite the scandalous expression you've got there... Are you sure you're not drunk, with how red your face is~?
403033.touch: Pfft... You're just too cute when you act all bashful but still can't resist trying to ogle me, ahaha~!
403033.login: Commander, did you come to have a drink?
403033.battle: Tsk... These fools need to learn how to read a room.
403033.main: Compared to those other stuffy, teetotaling banquets, something a bit more... liberated like this one is much more enjoyable. Don't you agree, Commander? |So, what do you like about me? My personality... or my body? If you lie, I'll make you take a shot~ |The Sakura Empire's liquors certainly have a distinctive flavor, but when a girl wants to cut loose, it's gotta be one of the classics~
403033.unlock: ... Huh? Commander, is that you? Me, drunk? No way... *hic*... If I was, Commander, then what are you planning to do to me? Hehe...
403033.drop_descrip: ... Huh? Commander, is that you? Me, drunk? No way... *hic*... If I was, Commander, then what are you planning to do to me? Hehe...
403033.home: Come on, don't be so tense. Just let go and relax.

10700040.detail: You'd like to chat with me? Of course we can do that. Please, have a seat.
10700040.touch: My luck forecast for today is... Oh? Would you like your fortune read too, Commander?
10700040.login: Good morning, Commander. Let's have a good day of work, shall we?
10700040.battle: Fighting is by no means my forte, but I'll do the best I can.
10700040.hp_warning: I must finish what I set out to do...!
10700040.feeling2: What is it, Commander? ...Ah, you found my lost handkerchief? Thank you so much.
10700040.headtouch: My, oh my~ Is there something on your mind, Commander? I can lend an ear if you'd like to talk about it.
10700040.main: Some destroyers came up to me the other day and wouldn't let me leave until I played a game with them. Hehehe~ Everyone here are such lovely people.|I have a poor memory for directions, so I often get lost. I've already needed people to come find me several times at this port... It's quite awkward for me.|You have so many types of cuisine on offer in the cafeteria. And they all taste so delicious... I need to watch it so I don't overeat.
10700040.feeling5: Sorry that I always make you lead me around the port. I've just gotten so reliant on the comfort of having you show me the way when I get lost... Hehehe~
10700040.upgrade: Thank you for helping me grow, Commander.
10700040.unlock: Why hello, my name's Azusa Miura~ Um, this is a port, right? And these are... shipgirls? Um~ Where exactly am I?
10700040.feeling4: Oh, Commander, perfect timing. I had some free time and cooked up some food, but I wound up making way too much. Care to join me for dinner?
10700040.feeling1: Sorry, I just... I just don't know what to talk about with you.
10700040.propose: I don't know if it was my destiny to come here and meet you and the girls under your command, but I'm glad I did, and I'll treasure this memory always.
10700040.drop_descrip: Why hello, my name's Azusa Miura~ Um, this is a port, right? And these are... shipgirls? Um~ Where exactly am I?
10700040.skill: I hope you'll all enjoy this next song!
10700040.profile: My name is Azusa Miura. I decided to debut as an idol after graduating junior college. As for the specific reason why I chose this career... I suppose it was in hopes I'll one day find the person of my dreams.
10700040.touch2: Eek! What was that for, Commander?
10700040.mission: My, oh my. We still have work to do. Let's tackle them one at a time.
10700040.home: Welcome back, Commander. Would you like some tea and a snack while you rest?
10700040.win_mvp: We've finished! How is everyone? No bruises or scratches?
10700040.expedition: The commission team has returned to port. What diligent girls they all are.
couple_encourage: Oh dear. What is this place, Ritsuko?
Let's do our best, Chihaya!
Oh dear... Wait for me, Iori!
10700040.mail: A new letter has come in. Would you like me to go get it?
10700040.feeling3: Good day to you, Commander. I went for a stroll just today and got lost on the way... Would you please show me the way to the dormitory?
10700040.lose: Is everyone okay? We should find a safe place to retreat to, quick!

101370.detail: You need to give me good equipments~ This way, those mean aircrafts won’t hurt me anymore.
101370.touch: Huh? Are you praising me for switching everyone’s breakfast into homemade Italian spicy-sauce noodles~ Thank you Commander!
101370.login: Commander Commander, while you were away I secretly drizzled hot sauce on everyone’s food. But how come only my food is especially spicy... oh no... don’t knock me on the head...
101370.battle: The battle has started, I have to behave myself~
101370.hp_warning: It doesn’t matter, I am very lucky. We should... should be able to survive!
101370.feeling2: I’ve been to many places, seen a lot, do you want to listen to my tales, Commander?
101370.mission_complete: The mission has been successfully completed, Commander you’ve worked hard out there.
101370.main: Compared to running errands, it’s definitely better to stick together with Commander. | Hehe, I am full of luck as long as the Commander holds my hand~ | Commander, do you want me to put insects in your bed?
101370.feeling5: I want to stay longer at port, Commander don’t leave me, ok? ...（flick sleeves）.
101370.upgrade: My body is heating up, I’m getting stronger! (flick sleeves) I feel so agile now~
101370.unlock: Kalk, reporting in (flick sleeves) Commander, will you give me a high-five. As long as we high-five, we’re friends.
101370.feeling4: Commander Commander, seeing you this happy has also made me very happy!
101370.feeling1: Commander, don’t you like the ice cream I made with hot sauce... such a meanie.
101370.propose: Commander, reach your hands into my sleeves… hurry hurry, grab my hands, hold them. This will bring us luck. Hehe, I will always be happy with you in the days to come!
101370.drop_descrip: Benson class Destroyer— Kalk, hull number DD-611.
101370.skill: Let’s charge ahead against the roaring wind——
101370.profile: I am Benson class Destroyer, Kalk, hull number DD611. I run many errands for the Eagle Union, and I’ve been to many places as such. Although, I don’t really like all this running around… (whispers)
101370.touch2: ...Does this make you happy, Commander? (Tilts head)
101370.home: Commander, even if a typhoon is blowing our way, I will still accompany you all the way to safety!
101370.expedition: Commander, come get the spoils of war~
couple_encourage: Every Benson Class Destroyer, let’s go together!
101370.mail: Hurry up and check your mail!
101370.feeling3: Come come~ There’s a rabbit hidden in my sleeves. Commander, do you want to see a magic trick? Wow... how did Mr. Rabbit suddenly slip away?
101370.lose: Sigh... I hate it when I get injured, so annoying...

302080.detail: You're welcome to inspect the other stuff, but you'd be best off not casually touching my demonic raiments.
302080.touch: You want to duel me? Don't worry, I'll give you a handicap.
302080.login: Hurry up and make today's plans.
302080.hp_warning: Ahaha! Now you shall witness the form of a true demon!
302080.feeling2: You may look like someone who is too gentle to hurt a fly, yet you have control over this entire port. I'm a little interested in you.
302080.headtouch: Don't go around touching my head.
302080.mission_complete: Accept these rewards. You've earned this privilege.
302080.main: Somebody I can't stand? I guess that'd be Nagara. She's the– Whuah, Nagara?! W-Wait, don't get any closer! MMPH, URMMMPHHH!|A new model of oxygen torpedo...? I say, do get me one of those. I promise I'll draw out every bit of its power. |My cloak's pretty cool? Heh~ you think so too, huh? ...Hey, stop trying to slack off!
302080.feeling5: I feel like I can entrust myself to you. Is this where the demon finally finds her home...? Commander, if I was to become the blade you wield, how would you use it?
302080.upgrade: I won't be able to test whether or not this strengthening worked outside of live combat.
302080.unlock: I'm Kinu. If you want this demon to do your bidding, then you'd better show me what you're capable of!
302080.feeling4: How about letting me treat you to a couple cups of sake tonight? Hah, don't worry, I just want to have a normal chat. Having a heart-to-heart over some fine spirits... what greater comfort in life is there?
302080.feeling1: Cowards shall never control a demon.
302080.propose: Commander, you are the worthy one who has conquered a demon. Let us commemorate today's vow, and aim for greater strength together.
302080.drop_descrip: Nagara-class light cruiser number five – Kinu.
302080.profile: I am the Nagara-class light cruiser, Kinu. My name derives from Kinugawa, meaning "furious and violent like a demon's wrath." I live up to my name, but trust me - that is not something that you would want to see.
302080.touch2: Really? Are you trying to get me mad?
302080.mission: Don't forget about your missions. A soldier must fulfill the orders of their superiors.
302080.home: You look like you're in a good mood. Are you the type that gets motivated the more you work?
302080.win_mvp: Make an enemy of me, and your defeat is already ensured.
302080.expedition: The commission team must be getting impatient from waiting.
couple_encourage: Be careful; don't let your guard down.
Hey Aoba, don't make me carry you back again.
Want to lend me your torpedo next time?
302080.mail: I've already highlighted the important parts for you, Commander.
302080.feeling3: I've heard that Yuubari is responsible for developing new equipment. If possible, could you ask her to upgrade my equipment? For example, starting with my torpedoes...

403032.detail: Frohes neues Jahr~ This is how we say we say "Happy New Year" in the Iron Blood.
403032.touch: You want to drink this? Not~ gonna~ share~
403032.mission_complete: Commander, did the rewards have any tasty drinks?
403032.main: Commander~ let's have a drink~ and two more drinks~ ahh... let's keep going~ |Hey Commander, why don't we call everyone over and drink together~ |The Sakura Empire's sake is truly delicious~ Next time, why don't we ask those stingy girls to let us try some liquor from the Eastern Radiance~
403032.unlock: So this is the Sakura Empire's New Year? Hehe, how interesting~ Commander, since it's the New Year, why don't you put aside all those papers and have a drink with me?
403032.drop_descrip: So this is the Sakura Empire's New Year? Hehe, how interesting~ Commander, since it's the New Year, why don't you put aside all those papers and have a drink with me?
403032.mail: New Year's greetings, huh? Aren't you the popular one~

105070.detail: You can look all you want. Just don't forget about your job.
105070.battle: March through the gates of hell! May our image be burned into the eyes of our enemies!
105070.feeling2: My motto is, 'survival of the fittest'
105070.main: Commander! If you don't sortie, I'll bring the girls and head to new waters myself!|I totally cannot comprehend why you're so easygoing...|The secret to getting a better figure?... Cease with such jokes.
105070.feeling5: I'm used to your pace now after all this time. I've yet to get used to staying in a room all day... If anything happens to me because of this, it's all on you. Don't tell me you're gonna dodge the issue.
105070.upgrade: Like a full score and then some... Not bad.
105070.unlock: You're the Commander? Hmm... Looks like you have potential. I'm motivated enough to help with your dreams. Ah, that reminds me, I am Tennessee. Got it memorized?
105070.feeling4: You're looking good these days. Hmm? Ah, not to worry. I've always stuck around with you. I don't want all the training to be in vain, after all.
105070.propose: If I take this, it means I'm yours forever? Fine, but on one condition; I want none of that 'You'll get hurt if you're in the battlefield' crap. I need some action every now and then!
105070.drop_descrip: Tennessee-class battleship –  Tennessee, Hull Number BB-43!
105070.profile: I am the new type of battleship, Tennessee. In terms of combat, my waterline protection and hull armor have been upgraded, and my fire control systems have improved my fighting capabilities further. Commander, your orders?
105070.touch2: I'm not a 'Clear' target like in a game!
105070.mission: Hurry and take care of the missions, will you?
105070.win_mvp: This kind of battle is quite good
105070.expedition: The commission team is back? Allow me to show how they should really be handled.
105070.feeling3: Commander, you are still too weak. Come and train with me, and I will turn you into a proper Commander!
105070.lose: Yes. Yes! This is the kind of challenge I'm looking for!

301832.detail: You feel a sense of relief when you see me? I'm not quite sure what you mean by that, but I'm glad that you're happy...
301832.touch: It's not time for the party yet...? Then, um, let's stay like this for a bit longer...
301832.login: Commander, did you come just to see me...? Ohh, for the first thing I see when I wake up to be you... I must be dreaming...!
301832.mission_complete: Great job on finishing your mission, Commander! Um, ahem! Don't you want to cuddle up with my big, fluffy tail...?
301832.main: My tail is fluffy and warm, and you can even use it as a blanket... At least, that's what Oyashio and the others keep saying. Would you like to give it a try, Commander?|Commander, whenever I gaze at you, whenever I talk to you, I feel so at ease that I could go to sleep... Hm? You feel the same way about me?|This outfit feels a bit tight around the chest... Um, Commander, p-please don't stare at me so much...
301832.feeling5: Commander, are you happy? ...I don't mean like in general, but... like, when we're together... Um... As for me, when it's just the two of us, I feel amazingly happy...♡
301832.unlock: There's still some time before the banquet begins, and I'm afraid I'm feeling a little sleepy... W-would you mind if I took a nap? Thank you...
301832.drop_descrip: There's still some time before the banquet begins, and I'm afraid I'm feeling a little sleepy... W-would you mind if I took a nap? Thank you...
301832.mission: Commander, your missions are of utmost importance... Mm, so I'll wait for you right here...
301832.home: Do you like it when I massage your back with my feet like this, Commander? ...Not in that sense? I see... I don't really get it though...
301832.expedition: Commander, our friends have returned from their commission. Sh-should we head down to welcome them back?
301832.mail: We've got new mail. I'm sure it's good news.

408060.detail: You know about those Union girls who call themselves "Solomon Knights" or something? Well, it has a nice ring to it... All righty, Commander, I'm an "Undersea Knight" from now on, got it?
408060.touch: Hop on, Commander, and make sure to hold on to my waist tight! It won't be my fault if you fall off~
408060.login: Commander, just hit me up next time and I'll give you a ride, okay?
408060.hp_warning: Looks like I've gotta pick up the pace...!
408060.feeling2: When I put in my headphones and rev the engines, I can outrun all my worries. Lemme tell you, Commander, it's one hell of a feeling.
408060.main: Ah, Commander, wait just a sec. I've gotta finish fine-tuning Great Shark. We can go afterwards. |Great Shark is land-capable, you know. Well, just not as fast. Don't ask why it works that way! |What kind of music do you like to listen to on trips, Commander? Have any recommendations?
408060.feeling5: Commander, look who's back! Hehe, seems like you've fallen in love with Great Shark, huh? All right, get on. Today, I'm going to show you a real special place!
408060.upgrade: I feel the need for speed!
408060.unlock: Hey! You! That commander over there! How 'bout coming for a ride on my Great Shark? I'll show you a real thrillin' time!
408060.feeling4: Commander, hurry up and hop on! There's a school of incredibly rare and beautiful fish passing by today! Who knows how long we'd have to wait if we missed this opportunity!
408060.feeling1: I'm going for a ride! Tschüss~
408060.propose: Don't worry, Commander. As long as you're somewhere Great Shark can get to, call me any time. I swear I'll come for you!
408060.drop_descrip: Iron Blood Type VIIC submarine – U-101.
408060.profile: I'm U-101, one of the Iron Blood's 7th U-Boat Flotilla. I took part in four wolfpack operations. You could say that disrupting the enemy supply lines is my specialty - I even received a Knight's Cross! My hobby is going on long rides with Great Shark. Commander, wanna come with me?
408060.mission: You have a new task? Want me to take you to where you need to go?
408060.home: Commander, want me to drop you off at the dorm so you can get some rest?
408060.expedition: The commission fleet is back? All righty, I'll go pick 'em up!
408060.mail: Hello! Your local courier U-101 has new mail for you~ Hahaha!
408060.feeling3: Y'know, I really want to have an all-out race with the other factions' subs. I just know it's gonna get my blood pumping! How about it, Commander, wanna do me a favor?
408060.lose: Couldn't get out of the way in time...

302081.detail: What Takao is doing can't be considered a club activity... No, I didn't mean anything by it. I just do what I like.
302081.touch: These little manjuu hardly make for good sparring partners. How about taking their place?
302081.login: Just finished my daily practice swings. Time to get back to work.
302081.main: Unless you are a genius, you can never depart from the fundamentals. Even if you are a genius, you cannot afford to neglect the fundamentals either. That is the nature of swordsmanship. |Prince of Wales and Repulse, huh? ...Hmph. I'd never call them cowards. |Isuzu clearly is also an oni, but she's somehow afraid of ghosts. Me...? Guh, I suppose I can't deny that...!
302081.unlock: Grr! What are you here for? Speak up. ...Oh, you just wanted to take a tour of the club activities? Sorry 'bout that, I don't like getting disturbed in the middle of this kind of training.
302081.drop_descrip: Grr! What are you here for? Speak up. ...Oh, you just wanted to take a tour of the club activities? Sorry 'bout that, I don't like getting disturbed in the middle of this kind of training.
302081.home: Calligraphy and swordsmanship both hone the body and the mind. Commander, how'd these words come out?
302081.win_mvp: Sorry, but these riggings are the real deal.
302081.mail: You've received a lot of New Year's greetings, Commander. Remember to take a look at them.

207010.detail: There are many Royal Navy ships named "Eagle," and I will go great lengths to maintain its honourable reputation.
207010.touch: What is it? An invitation to get lunch? Hmm... Sorry, but could you go in my place?
207010.login: Great to see you! Based upon your punctuality, I can already tell that you're a responsible commander.
207010.battle: The battlefield... Heh, I'm getting all fired up!
207010.hp_warning: A warrior of the Royal Navy won't back down so easily!
207010.feeling2: People say I'm not great at socializing, a fact that I begrudge. But my social skills aside, I do know my manners.
207010.mission_complete: Now that's the face of an accomplished commander. Good job.
207010.main: Let's see what's on the menu today... Fruits and a vegetable salad. Ideal for a low-calorie diet.|How much do I weigh? Ahem, you'd better drop this topic, or else...! Okay, I'm just exaggerating. But I hope you understand that it's a sensitive topic for me.|A band of Iron Blood submarines ran away before I could as much as say hello. Again... Guess I'll have to come up with a good way of approaching them.
207010.feeling5: You are irreplaceable to me. Whatever becomes of me... Scratch that. I'll stay the way I am now, just for you. Because I think this is what made me equally irreplaceable to you. Am I right?
207010.upgrade: Enhancements, huh... I just wish they wouldn't affect my weight...
207010.unlock: The name is Eagle. I intend to serve your fleet to the utmost of my abilities as a proud warrior of the Royal Navy.
207010.feeling4: Despite my low-calorie diet and daily rigorous exercise, my weight stays the same... *sigh*, I guess my past status as a battleship defines me more than I think... But why?! How does everyone else manage to lose weight just fine?!
207010.feeling1: You're betraying everyone's trust in you by acting like this. Pull yourself together, for god's sake!
207010.propose: I once met my final obstacle in the Suez Canal... But if you ever need saving, I will overcome any obstacle to get to you, Commander. This is my promise not just as a warrior, but as your lover.
207010.drop_descrip: Eagle-class light aircraft carrier – Eagle (HMS Eagle.)
207010.profile: After having been converted from a battleship into an aircraft carrier, I provided much early experience for the Royal Navy's carrier forces, and my final moments were spent fighting on the battlefield. Though I met a noble warrior's end, I do wish I'd been done in by a cannon or an airstrike, rather than a submarine.
207010.touch2: You see, this is the reason why we have to teach people proper etiquette.
207010.mission: There's still unfinished missions, Commander. We should get them done sooner rather than later.
207010.home: My body weight's still the same as it w– Oh! Commander! Didn't think you'd be back so soon. A-anyway, you'd better give our next mission plan a look!
207010.win_mvp: To show compassion to your foe is to put the safety of your allies at risk.
207010.expedition: Commission complete. Let's go and offer the returning team some biscuits. Don't worry about me, I can do without.
couple_encourage: Let us fight side by side!
Hrmh! Try as you wish, you won't beat me!
207010.mail: There's mail for you. Don't forget to give it a look.
207010.feeling3: I'm not a frequent attendee at Royal Navy tea parties... Which isn't to say I don't want to, it's just... they bring out snacks at tea parties... What do you think I mean, Commander?! I'd gain weight, that's the problem! ...Sorry, I lost my cool for a sec there.
207010.lose: Tsk, I've taken damage after fighting for so long... I'll need repairs when we return.

102092.detail: Ah, don't you worry, Commander. Your invitation's got top priority to me.
102092.touch: What's up, Knight? ... A rose...? Just what I needed! Here, Commander. A little gift from me to you, darling.
102092.login: Ready yet, Commander? It's time to go to the party!
102092.battle: Let's finish this in a flash!
102092.main: You wanna come to the party too, Knight? All right... you're coming, too!|Quite a few people have asked me for a dance, but I'm not a great dancer... Commander, could ya help me learn the basics of dancing?|*Phew*... You wanna go for something to eat when the party's over, Commander? I'll treat you, so don't be shy! I mean come on, we're friends~
102092.feeling5: Honestly, what with how people treat me when I wear this tuxedo, for a moment I considered acting more like a boy... But nah! In the end, it's obvious nothing beats being with you, Commander!
102092.unlock: Why am I stuck with this tuxedo when everyone else is wearing a dress?! ... Though it does feel slick, so I guess it's pretty nice. So, weren't we gonna go to the party, Commander? Then it's about time we head out!
102092.drop_descrip: Why am I stuck with this tuxedo when everyone else is wearing a dress?! ... Though it does feel slick, so I guess it's pretty nice. So, weren't we gonna go to the party, Commander? Then it's about time we head out!
102092.skill: Here's a present for you party poopers!
102092.mission: Commander, let's wrap up those missions pronto before the party starts!
102092.home: Let me join for the next sortie, Commander. It's not my style to just sit on my butt and wait around!
102092.mail: Hm? You brought the Commander's mail, Knight? Aren't you a clever dog! Good boy!

405021.detail: Commander, enjoy yourself to the fullest. Our hard-fought battles are for the sake of peaceful moments like these... and our hard-earned breaks provide us with will to keep fighting.
405021.touch: It's a bit stuffy... Commander, would you mind turning up the air conditioner?
405021.login: Commander, there's no need to rush yourself. There is meaning in simply waiting for you.
405021.main: As long as you're by my side, even looking off into the horizon is meaningful. |Some of my colleagues seem to mistake me for some unapproachable ice queen... Perhaps playing beach volleyball with them would help... |The sunset and the beach at night are wonderful views. When you're done with work, want to accompany me for a walk along the shore?
405021.unlock: In the past, I never saw summer as more than a hot and humid slog... But now? My outfit probably says it all... Let's go, everyone's already waiting for us at the beach.
405021.drop_descrip: Summer... In the past, it was always just a hot and stifling season... But now...? Doesn't my outfit tell the whole story? Let's get going, there's bound to be a lot of people on the beach.
405021.touch2: Even though it's summer... there are still some things you shouldn't do...
405021.mission: Even I can't get fired up about doing missions during the summer... because it's too hot...

102030.detail: This information is confidential, so please keep it a closely guarded secret.
102030.touch: Are you interested in my tanned skin, Commander?
102030.login: You came just in time. A few files need your signature.
102030.battle: Fire at will! I have you covered!
102030.feeling2: Commander, my responsibility is to ensure that you have the upper hand in foreign affairs. Rest assured, I am an expert in that area.
102030.mission_complete: Here is a summary of the rewards. Your confirmation, please, Commander.
102030.main: It's important to communicate with other nations.|Please don't stare at me in such a weird way.|I may be a diplomat, but don't even think about underestimating my power.
102030.feeling5: I wish to fight only for you, to give you the upper hand... Maybe I am no longer suited to be the entire fleet's diplomat.
102030.upgrade: Power is the foundation of gunboat diplomacies. Thank you.
102030.unlock: I am Brooklyn. I am an elite cruiser, so you may let me handle all foreign diplomacy matters.
102030.feeling4: Commander, a diplomat doesn't usually take on the role of a secretary... but I personally wish to deepen my relationship with you.
102030.feeling1: Commander, I'm thinking of resigning because you just don't seem like you're worth the effort.
102030.propose: Thank you, now I have more confidence in managing the fleet's affairs. Hm? I may act on your behalf for a little? What a pleasant joke. ... At any rate, I will not let you down.
102030.drop_descrip: Brooklyn-class Light Cruiser – Brooklyn, Hull Number CL-40!
102030.skill: Deterrence is also a part of diplomacy...
102030.profile: As the representative of the then newly constructed pre-war cruisers, I was put in charge of foreign diplomacy. That said, my firepower is never to be underestimated, so please put your mind at ease.
102030.touch2: A diplomat is not the same thing as a secretary... Please, restrain yourself, Commander!
102030.mission: Completing missions is a good way to demonstrate our capabilities. Please take a look at some of the new missions.
102030.home: Good work, Commander. I will make sure that the results of your last battle come to good use.
102030.win_mvp: Now then, let us talk about reparations.
102030.expedition: Though it may be tough for everyone, completing commissions like this will help raise our reputation. Let's start another one as soon as possible.
102030.mail: There's mail for you, Commander... Hm? Where was this sent from?
102030.feeling3: It feels like I've been managing your personal affairs more than foreign affairs lately, Commander... Surely this isn't on purpose, is it?
102030.lose: Now we won't have an advantage during the negotiations...

202029.detail: Look, Commander! There's a gorgeous sheila in the sky! ... Really? You believed that?
202029.touch: Let's go and sail off into the sunset! Strewth, this is what being a teeny's all about, eh~
202029.login: Commander, want some honey? It's heckin' yummy~!
202029.main: nil|Being here now, I can chat with anyone whenever! Stoked as a stove, I am!☆|You trying to hide some good chow from me? C'mon, let me have a taste!☆
202029.unlock: The cute and charming Achilles is Super☆Retro☆Fitted! Even my heel won't give me any problems now! Well, not like it really ever did before, ahaha~☆
202029.drop_descrip: The cute and charming Achilles is Super☆Retro☆Fitted! Even my heel won't give me any problems now! Well, not like it really ever did before, ahaha~☆
couple_encourage: Ajax, whaddya want me to do?

299041.detail: Artificial waves? Hmm, this might be more fun than I thought. Time to show off my swimming skills!
299041.touch: Ooh, my shoulders were starting to get a little stiff. You're not half-bad, eh~
299041.login: I heard this is a nice place to swim. Imagine my surprise to learn it wasn't a beach, but an outdoor pool... Still, I guess if we're just killing time, this is as good a place as any...
299041.main: C-could you stop staring at me like that? You're starting to weird me out...|Hahah, seems like this manjuu needs some more practice if it's struggling with these meager waves!|*sigh*... I'm not feeling satisfied yet. Guess I'll go for another swim...
299041.unlock: Phew... Swimming like this doesn't feel all that refreshing... Hey, how about you stop staring and come join me?
299041.drop_descrip: Phew... Swimming like this doesn't feel all that refreshing... Hey, how about you stop staring and come join me?
299041.home: Good exercise followed by some exquisitely cool watermelon, man, it's just the best! Hey, you'd better get over here and have a bite, or I'll finish this whole thing by myself!

405020.login: Once you get used to waiting, you lose sight of what you were waiting for.
405020.battle: Commander, I shall fight for your sake.
405020.hp_warning: No one would protect those who asked for their own destruction.
405020.feeling2: I have already grown used to the cold solitude of the North. At this point, it's natural for me to have no expectations.
405020.main: Big sister... Now that you mention it, I think I might actually have one... Ah... I've already started to forget.|Can you comprehend how it feels to watch the battlefield from afar, unable to do anything but lament the cruelty of war?|Strategic reasons? I was installed with cannons... but they were never meant to be fired. Ironic, isn't it?
405020.feeling5: Ahh... I see. I thought I was used to the cold and embraced it, but that was just because I had forgotten the joy of human interaction and the warmth of being with someone... But now I remember...
