405020.upgrade: If you have no opponents, all the might in the world is meaningless.
405020.unlock: I was imprisoned in the north for so long, unable to return home, and now you want me to follow you? ...Very well. It is up to you to show me the world.
405020.feeling4: The worst feeling in the world is not knowing whether to continue waiting or to give up hope. Commander, are you someone worth waiting for?
405020.feeling1: In the end... are you just another incompetent fool, unable to command me?
405020.propose: Ahh... so this is the warmth of one's beating heart... It's melting the cold and despair remaining within me. Danke sehr, Commander. The "Queen of the North" is no longer alone.
405020.profile: It's a bit hot... Ah, sorry. I am Tirpitz. Because I was stuck in the north by myself for so long, people suddenly started calling me the "Lone Queen of the North." If you think it's a good nickname, then you do not fully understand... how soulless those words are.
405020.touch2: I'll think of how to deal with you later.
405020.mission: Finish your missions properly. Perhaps you will one day realize the joy of having any purpose at all.
405020.home: Commander, you should show your face on the battlefield more often. If you stay behind your desk for too long, you may one day forget the meaning of life.
405020.win_mvp: So this... is the taste of victory.
405020.expedition: The commission seems to be complete... Next time, why don't you let me go? I'm a little curious.
405020.mail: More mail for you... Ah, I'm envious.
405020.feeling3: Those who have nothing to lose also have nothing to fear... But is this kind of bravery really anything to be proud of?
405020.lose: So this is... the frustration that comes from failure and fear.

308041.detail: Which subjects am I good at? I'd say I'm pretty decent at all of them. Ehehe, I did say you can leave everything to me.
308041.touch: Haah... as long as you're by my side, I feel safe and sound.
308041.login: D-deep sea fish, attack! Umm, uh... that's not how it works...? I don't seem to be very good at this...
308041.main: Coral reefs are breathtakingly beautiful, Commander. If you ever want to see for yourself, just let me know. |This might sound strange coming from me, but forest fires are a very serious matter. There will be dire consequences if you don't take that to heart. Just ask the girls of the Eagle Union. |There's nothing wrong with I-19, right... The next time I-26 calls everyone to play, I'll go check on her.
308041.unlock: Hi there, Commander. Oh, this outfit? I'll be wearing it to school today. By the way, did you want to come sit in on my class?
308041.drop_descrip: Hi there, Commander. Oh, this outfit? I'll be wearing it to school today. By the way, did you want to come sit in on my class?
308041.home: Uuhh... the whole time during class, I was thinking about when you'd come back, Commander... Looks like I-26 is going to make fun of me again...

301020.detail: Why does everyone want to touch my ears? What's so special about them...?
301020.touch: Is there something you want to talk about, Commander?
301020.login: I see, so that's how your footsteps sound... I'll commit it to memory.
301020.battle: I have a little experience with leading a fleet, but...
301020.feeling2: I've not heard anything suspicious today... And that's a good thing.
301020.mission_complete: That noise... Sounds like our rewards are here.
301020.main: I like the scritchy-scratchy noise paper makes when you write on it. It's relaxing.|Fubuki's always bursting with energy whenever I see her. I'm honestly impressed with her...|A carrot? Uhh, no thanks? What do you think I am? A rabbit?
301020.feeling5: Can I snuggle you up for a minute? Thanks... I can hear your heart going ba-thump, ba-thump. It's really soothing~
301020.upgrade: Motivation overclocked! ...Is what Fubuki would say, I bet.
301020.unlock: Fubuki-class number two, Shirayuki. I'm a bit quieter than my elder sister... Mm, pleased to meet you.
301020.feeling4: We could share an umbrella on a rainy day, go for a walk, and just listen to the sound of the raindrops... Hm? Did I say something out loud just now?
301020.feeling1: I, I don't want to hear your noise...
301020.propose: Is your heart racing, Commander? That's okay, because mine is too. Hehehe~ So, do you promise to always, always be with me? You're not going to regret it? Great! Then we're wed now!
301020.drop_descrip: Special Type I-class destroyer number two – Shirayuki.
301020.profile: I'm Shirayuki, Fubuki-class destroyer number 2. I served Destroyer Squadron 3 during the war, and... that's pretty much all I have to say. I'll make myself useful to you and the rest of the fleet.
301020.touch2: Wh-what do you think you're doing?!
301020.mission: More new missions... Ugh... Could I call over Fubuki for some extra help?
301020.home: *clap* *clap*... I'm glad you're back. Let's have some tea together.
301020.win_mvp: It's over? Phew... Looks like everyone's okay, too.
301020.expedition: Sounds like the commission team has returned to port. I heard their footsteps.
couple_encourage: Oh, Fubuki. So full of energy.
You're from... Planet Bunny?
Ready for your orders!
301020.mail: Here's your letter. You should read it before it becomes old news.
301020.feeling3: I don't like crowds. All the noise they make gives me headaches... I much prefer quiet places.
301020.lose: They beat us... I'll cover our retreat!

101301.detail: I wonder if Radford would be happy to wake up to an apple in her present box... M-Maybe I should give her some candy, after all...?
101301.touch: You know... It's okay to come a b-bit closer...?
101301.login: The code word... do you remember it? I'm so glad... Commander, Merry Christmas!
101301.battle: I won't hand these important presents over... Hah!
101301.main: Santa would be wearing a Santa hat and a beard like I am, right?|Nicholas is acting just the same as she would on any other day, even though it's Christmas...|It's a shooting star! If you make a wish upon it before it disappears...! Uh, you want to know what I wished for...? I-It's a secret!
101301.unlock: Commander, g-good evening...? Right now, I'm bringing presents to Radford and the others...? Could you give me a hand? Th-thank you... Um, your present.. this apple, do you want it?
101301.drop_descrip: Commander, g-good evening...? Right now, I'm bringing presents to Radford and the others...? Could you give me a hand? Th-thank you... Um, your present.. this apple, do you want it?
101301.touch2: C--Commander... N-Not in the dark like this... Ah...
101301.home: You're working so hard even though it's Christmas Eve... Commander... You all... Good job...!

308040.detail: Sorry to bother you when you're busy, Commander, but could you please help me test the capabilities of my seaplane?
308040.touch: Haah... I'm being filled to the brim with your energy, Commander...
308040.login: Mmh... Welcome back, Commander. While you were gone, I finished compiling all the reports. Here you go~
308040.battle: Sometimes, you've got to stand out!
308040.hp_warning: Now, this is a bit of a sticky situation...
308040.feeling2: Commander, thank you for coming to see me today. Because of you, I'll have some extra spring in my step. Hehe~
308040.mission_complete: These are the fruits of everyone's efforts. Make sure to receive them with pride.
308040.main: Where I'm from, we always offer our respects for the food in front of us before each meal. It's a custom that helps us be at ease. |I hope my sister hasn't been causing too much trouble for you. She's a little ball of energy... there's no way I can keep up with her... |Commander... Commander...? Are you still asleep? I'm getting a bit worried...
308040.feeling5: Ahhn... Commander, you've come to see me again... Today... today, you won't leave my side this time, right? Commander, if you stay with me, I'll never be lonely ever again!
308040.upgrade: Hehe... Thank you for helping me become even more reliable, Commander~
308040.unlock: Phew... I finally found you! Commander, I'm I-25. I hope that I can be a big help to you. Anyway, it's nice meeting you~
308040.feeling4: Commander, sorry to call you out all of a sudden, but I've just been so lonely... I'm quite bold, you say? Ehehe... Well, you know, I did have a bit of experience getting... tangled up with the enemy back then. Want to hear more about it?
308040.feeling1: Though I am very sorry that it has come to this, I must once again remind you that your poor work ethic has already affected the fleet.
308040.propose: This is the proof of our oath to each other, Commander... Thank you so much! Finally, I've found my happiness! I'm so glad... we'll get to spend all our days together like this from now on! Ehehe~♪
308040.profile: I'm the Type-B class cruiser submarine, I-25. I'm at my best when it comes to reconnaissance and disrupting shipping routes. I've also been in some... pretty daring operations. Hehe~ Commander, you can count on me.
308040.touch2: Commander, do you... like this kind of sensation...?
308040.mission: There are still some missions that need to be completed. Commander, let's finish them together.
308040.home: Judging by your grin, Commander, you must've had a resounding victory. Hehe, why don't you come here and let me massage your shoulders?
308040.win_mvp: Heehee, from now on, just leave it to me~
308040.expedition: Everyone in the commission fleet has returned safely. Hmm... should I reward them with some homemade chocolate?
couple_encourage: Try not to get lost, all right?
308040.mail: New mail keeps piling up... Commander, you should hurry up and start getting through these...
308040.feeling3: ...Is Commander really not coming today..? I'm going to die of loneliness... ... C-Commander?! Did you hear me just now??

301269.detail: Here you go, Commander. Um, your tea! It's Ariake's favorite kind, but I do not know if it will be to your liking or not...
301269.main: I feel like I've gotten a little taller after my retrofit... and it makes Ariake seem shorter in comparison... Ugh...|(whispers) Hatsushimo, you'll trouble Commander if you do that! ...I-I wasn't saying anything!|Wakaba, Commander, I have some walnut daifuku for you. Um, huh...? You don't need the wrapping...?
301269.feeling5: The gentle sea breeze, the warm sunlight, and the sound of waves upon the beach... Every day here at port is filled with happiness, because I can be together with both you and Ariake...
301269.unlock: Ariake-class destroyer, Yuugure, has completed retrofitting. Ehehe, from now on... Ariake and I will be in your care once more, Commander.
301269.drop_descrip: Ariake-class destroyer, Yuugure, has completed retrofitting. Ehehe, from now on... Ariake and I will be in your care once more, Commander.
301269.home: Welcome back, Commander. I'm preparing tea for Ariake, so please wait a moment for me to bring you yours.
301269.win_mvp: Ariake, Commander, I did it! Mhm... I really won!
301269.expedition: A commission has been completed. Commander, please make sure to stockpile our resources for construction.

202030.detail: Commander, do you want to know more about my secrets...?
202030.touch: Alright. If you make me feel good, I might 'allow' you something~
202030.login: Hehe. I'll be having your care again for today, Com~man~der!
202030.battle: Oh my~ If you prostrate yourselves before me, I might show you mercy
202030.feeling2: You have good eyes... Alright. Then you will become my new little piggy. You don't have the right to refuse.
202030.mission_complete: Reward? Of course it refers to the mission reward, doesn't it? Now take it. Or are you expecting something special?
202030.main: Do you want to have a meal first, or a bath? Or do you want... *giggles*...|I'll tell you a secret... Lend me your ear... Pfft! Did that tickle?|When I see you daydreaming, I have this insatiable urge to step on your face...
202030.feeling5: I'm not a bad girl, you know? It's just I've never been serious before I met you. I've said this much, so now you're going to stick around, alright? You~ little~ piggy~?
202030.upgrade: *giggles* I will thank you af-ter this~
202030.unlock: Commander, I am the 3rd ship of Leander class light cruisers, Ajax. I'm quite famous despite how I look... Commander,
202030.feeling4: Do not worry. You are the only one who made me want to abuse you this much. That's right, you are like the fated person for me, Ajax~ Aren't you happy about that~
202030.feeling1: So you broke... Oh well. Time to find a new toy, I guess
202030.propose: This is... Looks like I have to prepare a new 'menu' of things. Please look forward to it, my lovely - little - piggy~
202030.drop_descrip: Leander-class light cruiser – Ajax, Hull Number 22!
202030.profile: I am Ajax of the Leander class ships. Commander, have you been to Plata river before? I have some wonderful memories there. Hehehe...
202030.touch2: When I think about perverts who touch 'that' spot, I want to step on them!
202030.mission: I'll give you a special reward once you finish this mission!
202030.home: *giggles* Little piggies that have exercised look so tasty, don't they.
202030.win_mvp: Commander, good work out there. You did well...
202030.expedition: Commander, I'll count to 5. If you don't greet the girls out for commissions by the time I'm done... *giggles*
couple_encourage: We'll beat them not with brute force, but with tactics.
I've got no interest in tying up my little piggy.
Can you have some fun while you're at it?
You've got excellent taste, Miss Formidable.
202030.mail: A mail. The contents? You'll tell me, right? Com~man~der
202030.feeling3: *giggles* I'm liking you more and more. I wonder if you can amuse me further, my cute little piggy~?
202030.lose: Tsk... I'll pay you back for this next time!

101371.detail: Cute little bunny~ Hehe, Commander, I like to hang out with cute little animals.
101371.touch: Want to come with me? Mhm, let's head to school together then!
101371.login: Commander, I've been waiting for you! Uuu.... just look, I've been standing here for so long that my cannon and torpedoes have turned into ice pops~
101371.main: It's snowing pretty hard outside. Commander, want a nice warm cup of cider before you head out?|Hobby is so cute, isn't she? I'd love to be as outgoing as her.|It's really cold outside, Commander, so you should take care to stay warm. Here, I poured your cider into hot sauce so it will keep you warm better~
101371.feeling5: Commander, you've worked so hard out there, so let's get you a fresh change of clothes. Let me massage your shoulders and make some warm cider for you~ (Shakes head) No, there's no hot sauce this time. Just lots and lots of sugar, hehe~
101371.unlock: Kalk, reporting in once again, now with a new outfit! Hehe... Commander, will you walk me to school?
101371.drop_descrip: Kalk, reporting in once again, now with a new outfit! Hehe... Commander, will you walk me to school?
101371.touch2: Commander? So you're also a prankster...
101371.home: Commander, take a break. I already made a snowman. Now, let's have a snowball fight~
101371.win_mvp: MVP? Hehe, thanks for everyone’s support.

301021.detail: Today it's my turn to look after the bunnies. No, I said "look after," not "be looked after by."
301021.touch: There's a lot you have to keep in mind when playing with a bunny. For starters...
301021.login: I recognize that sound. It's you, Commander! Heheh. I know it by heart.
301021.main: Maybe I should also bring some hay along with the carrots... No, Fubuki! You can't feed that stuff to a bunny!|I guess the ears really are the first thing people go for when they see a bunny... No, I'm talking about bunnies, not me!|Oh, to be a happy rabbit, spending my days eating, sleeping, and playing with humans...
301021.unlock: Whoa now! There's enough food for everyone, so don't fight over it! ...Commander? Don't just stand there, give me a hand, please!
301021.drop_descrip: Whoa now! There's enough food for everyone, so don't fight over it! ...Commander? Don't just stand there, give me a hand, please!
301021.home: Come here, little bunny. There, that's a good girl... Phew. Finally got them all to settle down.

107051.detail: Come to think of it, Enterprise did tell me not to drink the blue stuff like A MILLION TIMES. But like, what's the dig beal, Commander?
107051.touch: Hey, Commander, you wanna hear some EMBARRASSING stories about Enterprise and Hornet? Oh, you'd rather hear mine? Hehe, THAT can be arranged.
107051.login: You're late, Commander. You know what THAT means. One penalty drink!
107051.hp_warning: Urk. I feel... a little sick...
107051.mission_complete: Here's to a mission accomplished! CHEERS!
107051.main: Enterprise is a good girl. So's Hornet. And Hammann. They all found their PLACE in this fleet. But me? The big sister? I'm HAPPY for them. And a teeeensy bit lonely.|You know, Commander, looking back, I have some regrets. Like if I knew you were THIS good? I'd've been more HONEST with myself.|Oh! Is that my cute little Hammann?! When did you get so BIG?! ...Oh, you're the Commander, aren't you? Have you seen Hammann?
107051.feeling5: I mean, it's only natural for a good couple to be a little clingy, right? After all I've been through, I'm WAY too shy to make the first move. So that means YOU have to do it. Got it?
107051.unlock: Hey, Commander, are you lost? How about a drink? ... Huh? Drunk? Me? Oh, Commander, you're such a card. This is just grape juice... isn't it?
107051.drop_descrip: Hey, Commander, are you lost? How about a drink? ... Huh? Drunk? Me? Oh, Commander, you're such a card. This is just grape juice... isn't it?
107051.touch2: OH! Commander, at least buy me a drink first!
107051.mission: Now now, Commander, I'll be mad at you if you ditch these assignments.
107051.home: I'm not letting you leave until YOU have a drink with me, Commander.
107051.win_mvp: OOPSIE! What was that I just said in front of EVERYONE...?
107051.expedition: You wanna sneak off to the harbor? Ugh, I TOLD you already, Commander, I'm *hic* not as think as you drunk I am!
107051.mail: You can't go off with someone else until you finish drinking with ME, Commander!
107051.lose: I, I have a feeling... like all the clout I had as a big sister is COMPLETELY GONE... after tonight...

301580.detail: There is little I can do on my own. So, please, if I can assist in any way, don't be afraid to ask. I will help you.
301580.touch: Do you feel tired? Shall I give you a shoulder massage?
301580.login: You have returned, Commander. I have already sorted all your documents.
301580.battle: Be careful. Try to stay close to me.
301580.feeling2: Hm? I seem cold and distant to you? I've heard that from Harutsuki before... Oh, bother...
301580.mission_complete: I have brought the mission rewards. These should be all of them.
301580.main: Why I help people? I feel I should; therefore I do it... Is that strange?|Some have mistaken me for a light cruiser... I wonder why... I don't look like one...|"Forcing myself"? Not at all. If I were, my help would only have the opposite effect.
301580.feeling5: A "date"? What does that mean? ... It means we'll play together? Certainly, if that's what you wish. ... Why are you smiling? You're quite strange...
301580.unlock: I'm honored to meet you, Commander. I have come to assist you. From now on, I can help you with your work whenever needed.
301580.feeling4: You don't require my help, yet you keep me waiting by your side... Why is that? I don't quite understand...
301580.feeling1: I would prefer it if you'd stay away from me.
301580.propose: This is how you've felt about me, Commander...? I've been slow to catch on, haven't I... But, do not worry, I pledge myself to you. I swear to always protect you, do exactly as you wish, and never again leave your side.
301580.profile: I am the Akizuki-class destroyer Yoizuki. I specialize in anti-air combat. If you ever have any problems, please tell me. I will solve them quickly for you.
301580.touch2: Commander, are you asking for a beating?
301580.mission: We have received a mission. Is it something I may take care of?
301580.home: You must be tired. Should I prepare tea while you rest for a while, Commander?
301580.win_mvp: We have everyone to thank for this victory.
301580.expedition: A commission has been completed. Splendid work.
301580.mail: Commander, I have left your mail here.
301580.feeling3: I know that I can't always be by Harutsuki's side to help when she feels nervous. Yet, my body always acts on its own accord...
301580.lose: They tricked us... Everyone, retreat! I will watch your backs...!

405022.drop_descrip: I bet Bismarck must've been thinking about how to invite me to the party, but ended up asking you to do it, Commander. Hehe... Let's get going soon. It's best not to keep her waiting.

301581.detail: I received a good luck charm from Harutsuki... It's nice when someone offers you their blessings.
301581.touch: Commander, I'm completely soaked in sweat... You probably shouldn't touch me.
301581.login: I registered for several sporting events. I must give it my all so I won't slow down my teammates...
301581.main: Harutsuki, slow down and match your pace with mine... One, two! One two!|It's quite hot today, Commander. I brought a drink with me... I drank a little from it, but... would you like to have some?|Ugh... My hair is being annoying... Harutsuki's not here, either... Excuse me, Commander, could you give me a hand?
301581.feeling5: Will you enter with me for the three-legged race? Don't worry, we're unbeatable as a pair.
301581.unlock: It's my turn? Hold on... Umm, could you please not stare at me like that? It's... making me feel uncomfortable.
301581.drop_descrip: It's my turn? Hold on... Umm, could you please not stare at me like that? It's... making me feel uncomfortable.
301581.touch2: Are you taking advantage of me at a time like this? Are you mentally prepared for what comes next, Commander?
301581.home: All the entrants are strong candidates... I'll need to exert myself for the next event, too.

102093.detail: What kind of music do you like, Commander? I've gotta have the stuff that gets you pumped up.
102093.touch: Commander, you should pick out a bike too! Just leave the paint job to me, hehe!
102093.login: Ready to go, Commander? We're about to go chase the wind!
102093.main: I did this guy's paint job myself. Pretty sweet, huh? Hehe~ |Don't let the size fool you. This little guy has some serious kick! |Even when we're out for a spin, we have to observe the traffic rules. Safety first, after all~
102093.unlock: Good timing! I was just about to take my little buddy here out for a road trip! Commander, there's room for two if you want to come!
102093.drop_descrip: Good timing! I was just about to take my little buddy here out for a road trip! Commander, there's room for two if you want to come!
102093.home: Let's go outside and get some stretching in, Commander~

304070.detail: *cough*... *sniffle*... Ugh... I, I'm okay... I just ate too many sweets, and now I'm not feeling so good... *cough* *cough*... *sniffle*...
304070.touch: It's not that my clothes are slipping off, but... Oh, you don't want me catching a cold? Yes, I shall be mindful of that.
304070.login: Commander, I've put today's itinerary here as well as all the documents that need to be looked over. Hm...? I'm perfectly capable of handling this kind of workload by myself.
304070.hp_warning: Was there an error in my calculations...?
304070.feeling2: I shall do anything to protect Akagi, the Sakura Empire, and my friends here at this port. Commander, please give me your orders.
304070.mission_complete: Mission complete, Commander. When can I confirm our next mission?
304070.main: As expected of the head of the Royal Maids... Even I must stop to admire such an excellent cup of black tea... Mm~ hmm~|Akagi, Commander is your superior, not your subordinate. ...Jeez, if you end up causing even more trouble, you're going to get an earful!|Oops, I mistook the manjuus for dango again... It must be because I'm so hungry...
304070.feeling5: Commander, it's time to take a break. Though you're always looking out for my health, your words wouldn't be persuasive if you didn't also take care of yourself. Here, I've prepared the bed for you~
304070.upgrade: I must also become stronger, so that I can protect Akagi.
304070.unlock: Battlecruiser Amagi offers you her humble greetings, Commander. *cough* *cough* ...Ah, I'm fine, I just seem to have caught a little cold... *achoo!* Aww...
304070.feeling4: *Nom*... Shoooo yummy... Oh, Commander, my apologies, I was just eating this bit of mochi... Hm, it's okay to finish it first? If, if you say so...
304070.feeling1: Commander, are you going insane because of my recent poor health...?
304070.propose: You musn't, Commander... If you give this ring to me, then Akagi will... Huh, she's fine with it? ...I see, Akagi is all grown up as well... Wait, sorry, I should be focusing on giving you an answer first... But yes, it'd be an honor to accept this!
304070.drop_descrip: 1st Ship of the Amagi-class Battlecruisers, Amagi
304070.profile: I am Amagi, battlecruiser from the Sakura Empire. Commander, I hope to grow up big and strong here at this port so that I may protect you and Akagi. In other words... I'll do my best to eat properly and sleep properly.
304070.touch2: Hm? Commander, I am currently busy thinking.
304070.mission: Unfinished missions still remain. We must make efficient use of our earnings...
304070.home: Welcome back, Commander. Would you like to try some of our traditional sweets? ...If you'd like, I could also eat them with you.
304070.win_mvp: Now then... how shall we press the advantage? Hehehe...
304070.expedition: Commander, a commission has been completed. Should you be willing, may I propose a suggestion for our next task?
couple_encourage: Akagi, don't cause any trouble for the commander.
I'd better not catch you trying to intimidate the commander.
304070.mail: I wonder if there's any candy inside... Oh, it's just a regular letter...
304070.feeling3: You want to see me grow up healthy and strong? Umm... I understand the importance of this as your subordinate and ship, but... should I be doing anything special?
304070.lose: *cough* *cough*... I can't show something so unsightly to Akagi and the others...

403038.detail: In Ironblood, we also use animal nicknames to call our lovers, like teddy bear or little bunny or something else. So Commander, do you want me to call you teddy bear or little bunny?
403038.touch: I know what’s on your mind, Commander...but we need to focus on work right now.
403038.login: Commander, you did not happen to peek at other girls while on the way here, right? ~~
403038.main: Ugh... my body suddenly feels so weak... I’d only recover if you give me a kiss, Commander. | Don’t overstretch yourself at work ~ otherwise… my loneliness will drive me to tease you.| I feel so lucky right now --- why you ask? Take--a--guess, dear?
403038.unlock: If fate brought us together, then it has my thanks… I look forward to our future together~
403038.drop_descrip: If fate brought us together, then it has my thanks… I look forward to our future together~
403038.mission: All these missions….you pick Commander...I’m ready for them all~
403038.home: Commander, the bathtub has been filled with hot water, so who goes first, or…?
403038.mail: Receiving a lot of mails….after all, you're the Commander, a really popular one, huh.

102163.detail: This? Just a doodle, nothing of note... Please, would you stop trying to peek?
102163.touch: You'd like to see my notes? Sure thing, just– H-hey! I didn't say you could flip through it as you see fit!
102163.login: Fashionably late, I see. Had you turned up a moment later, I would've gone home for the day.
102163.main: Omaha! Don't you think the amount of snacks in your desk drawers is a little excessive?|Let's see what's new on Juustagram... Concord's posted a new sweets review. 101170.feeling4: I'm used to being alone... But I think I like it better when you're with me, Commander... Mmm... Zzzzzz...

303010.login: Commander, please be more careful when you open the door...

303010.feeling5: If you're okay with this... then I don't mind, Commander. But... I've never been in a relationship before, so I don't know what it's like. Can you teach me?
303010.unlock: Ah! Sorry for bumping into you... Huh? You're the Commander?! F-Furutaka, first ship of the Furutaka class, reporting for duty! Can you please forget what just happened? Ehehe...
303010.feeling4: Yeah... Being able to live with Kako and seeing my sisters from the Mikawa and 6th Fleet was always a dream of mine. Commander, you've made my dream come true. That's why... I'll do anything for you!
303010.feeling1: (Furutaka ignores you as she passes by)
303010.propose: I've never felt like this in my life before... But as long as I'm with you, I'll be able to feel this way more and more, right? I can't wait!
303010.drop_descrip: First ship of the {namecode:53}-class heavy cruisers, {namecode:53}.
303010.profile: I'm the Furutaka-class heavy... Err, just call me Furutaka! I may not look it, but I participated in the First Battle of the Solomon Sea! I also helped my sister Aoba out a lot! In the end though, I rushed too far ahead and didn't make it back myself... Ehehe...
303010.touch2: I never thought you'd take an interest in me, Commander... Frankly, I'm a bit happy~
303010.mission: A new mission, huh? Seems like it might be a bit tricky.

303010.mail: Sorry, Commander... I tripped and fell while getting the mail and now it's all wrinkled...
303010.feeling3: Commander~ Oww! ...Ehehe... Thanks, I almost fell again. I'm trying to pay more attention so that I don't trip as much, but I was so happy that I let my guard down.

301280.detail: Commander, don't I look ninja-like when I do this with my hands? Ehehe, that's because Kuro taught me~
301280.touch: Commander, isn't it amazing how nurturing Oyashio is? ... Er! I'm talking about the ocean current!

301280.feeling2: Commander, would you like to watch my show? By all means, come on over and take a seat~ The more the merrier, after all!

301280.main: Commander, will you come to watch my show when you have free time?|Kuro is my dear friend! Her namesake is obvious, isn't it? My oh so serious big sister!|Of course the strings are a puppetry thing. So why do I put torpedoes on them? Ahaha... Let's call it an old trade secret.
301280.feeling5: Commander, I thought it would be great to be as clear-headed as Kuroshio... But there's no way I could. I like Kuroshio, I like you, and I like puppet shows. That's just who I am.
301280.upgrade: Oooh! I just came up with a new idea for a show!
301280.unlock: My big sister is a ninja, and I'm a puppeteer. Isn't it amazing how diverse our world is~? I'm the fourth ship of the Kagerou-class, Oyashio. And with my puppet Kuro, I will dazzle you, Commander.
301280.feeling4: Commander, you're awesome. Not only do you know what I'm thinking, but you help me get through to everyone else... One day, I'm going to make Kuroshio laugh, and I know you'll definitely be there to see it!
301280.feeling1: No matter what you do, Commander, Kuroshio has no problem following you... But I'm not so forgiving. For her sake, Commander, en garde!
301280.propose: And so the Commander and Oyashio lived happily ever after for all the rest of their days... Ehehe, even if the audience might get sick of it, I'm hoping the rest of our story is a long, happy comedy♪
301280.skill: The fun has only just begun, right~♪
301280.profile: I'm the fourth ship of the Kagerou-class, Oyashio. I've always been close with Kuroshio. She can tell you everything you need to know, so just ask her~♪ Oh, unless...? You'd rather I act it out for you?
301280.touch2: Huh?! Grraagh! ... Oh, Commander, I'm sorry... that's just how we've been trained in this line of work...
301280.mission: Commander, let's go knock out one of those new missions~ I need to get some new material♪
301280.home: Kuro, why don't you give the Commander a massage? Yes, I think hopping around the shoulders should do the trick?

301280.mail: Commander, guess which torpedo has your mail in it? If you're wrong... well, it probably won't blow up♪
301280.feeling3: As a ninja, my sister is always very serious... And since I'm a puppeteer, I always thought it would be nice to make her laugh sometimes. That's kind of a tall order though, ahaha...
301280.lose: Ugh! Commander! Quickly, take the others and run!

202032.drop_descrip: I have some special chocolate right here, just~ for~ you. Hehe, if you want it so badly... then come and get it~

107050.detail: It's alright if you don't remember me...
107050.login: Greetings, Commander. If there's a problem, please leave it to me.
107050.hp_warning: The light is still far away...
107050.feeling2: I want to maintain the current superior-subordinate relationship, Commander... Don't mind me...

107050.feeling1: So you truly will leave me one day...
107050.propose: I had fallen into the darkness. It was you, Commander who gave me light and a helping hand which pulled me out of it. That's why this time, I, Yorktown, will give you my name. The name that shoulders the burden of liberty and peace...
107050.drop_descrip: Yorktown-class aircraft carrier ー Yorktown, Hull Number CV-5!
107050.profile:
Lead ship of the Yorktown class aircraft carriers, Yorktown. 
Abandoned...? It wasn't their fault, but I do not have the courage to reach out for light from that darkness. Will you leave me, Commander? Or will you guide me by my hand...?
107050.touch2: Are you truly prepared to leave your mark on someone like me?
107050.mission: Your new missions have been organized, Commander.
107050.win_mvp: If victory can bring peace, then I...!
107050.expedition: What's wrong, little eagle? So, the commission team has returned? Commander, let us greet them.
couple_encourage: Just because you speak like an adult doesn't mean you are one!
What a long overdue reunion!
Spread your wings and fly, Enterprise!
Commander, do you like to spoil your girls?
8 Talents? We're a pretty lively bunch!
107050.mail: My eagle got the mail. Please read it carefully.
107050.feeling3: Commander, you're weird... Even though I don't want to experience more painful departures, you keep stepping into my heart...

403040.detail: It's times like these... where I simply must punish you.
403040.touch: You just never learn, do you? Do you want to taste my whip again that badly~?
403040.login: You sure took your sweet time. Just where were you rooting around?
403040.battle: I'm going to enjoy mopping you all up~
403040.hp_warning: Do not underestimate the great Deutschland!
403040.feeling2: There is no thrill like waging war with a grin on your face! There's no way a lowly animal like you could ever understand that! Ahahahaha!
403040.mission_complete: Hurry up and fetch the rewards for me~
403040.main: It seems like I must speak in a way that even lowly animals can understand.|Hahaha! I didn't even need to fire my gun to scare off those cruisers~|If you insist on standing around like an idiot, I'm just going to leave.
403040.feeling5: For keeping me amused this long, I shall grant you the privilege of holding me. Why are you still standing there? Have you never heard of a princess carry? Princess~ carry!
403040.unlock: From now on, you are Deutschland's servant! You should feel honored. Also, don't answer me with "mhm." You will answer me with "yes, ma'am" from now on. Are we clear?
403040.feeling4: A lion doesn't concern itself with the bleating of sheep. But... I do find you interesting for a lowly animal. If you amuse me some more, maybe I will listen to your wishes.
403040.feeling1: I have no interest in you anymore... I should find myself a new pet.
403040.propose: I never thought the day would come when I pledge myself to a lowly animal. I've never felt anything like this before... but it's unexpectedly fun. Ahahaha~! From now on, you're my vehicle number two! You should be grateful!
403040.profile: Hmph! I'm Deutschland, the first ship of the Deutschland-class! A prestigious individual such as myself wouldn't be sent into smaller battles. As such, it's only natural that I don't have many of these petty achievements. It's called spiritual leadership! Hmph! Lützow? ...Shut up! Like I'd care about that!
403040.touch2: Hmm? It seems like you're enjoying yourself... do you get off to this kind of stuff?
403040.mission: Mission! There's no entry for "incomplete" in my dictionary!
403040.home: Pay attention, you idiot! Just because we're back at port doesn't mean that you're done.
403040.win_mvp: Even though the enemies were no big deal... what a pompous affair.
403040.expedition: Hmph, so our little lambs managed to complete their commission. What a pleasant surprise.
403040.mail: You've received a letter in that lowly animal language of yours. Fetch~
403040.feeling3: Lowly animal, root around for all you are worth to find something worthy of my attention. Ahahahaha~
403040.lose: I'd sink to the bottom of the ocean before surrending to you animals!

206051.touch: Commander, do you like my qipao? Don't you think blonde hair matches the aesthetic of the dress quite well? Ehehe~
206051.login: Hm? Commander, you're back~ Is there a story you'd like to hear from me today?
206051.mission_complete: Mhm! As expected, Commander, you've finished the mission! Hurry and see if we were rewarded with any tea~
206051.main: The Dragon Empery's traditional dances seem difficult to learn... Eh, you'd like to learn them with me? In that case, we should be able to learn them in no time~ |Eh, fireworks display? 206051.feeling1: I have a commander who is as bitter as oversteeped green tea that has been left out and forgotten.
206051.drop_descrip: Does this dress from the Dragon Empery not suit me well? Though I was born in the Eagle Union and raised by the Royal Navy, my time in the Dragon Empery also left a deep impression upon me. Why don't we have a chat about their profound culture and tea? Hehe~

206051.touch2: Oh dear... Commander, flirting is fine but please don't go overboard~
206051.lose: Ugh... there's this saying that "for soldiers, both victory and defeat are standard issue."

301840.touch: This marking on my right cheek? You haven't heard of it, Commander? It's the latest fashion trend! Here, I'll draw one on for you!
301840.login: Welcome back! ...Got any new jobs? I'm down for anything!

301840.hp_warning: The real fight's only getting started!

301840.headtouch: Look, fluffy and super pattable, right? ...Hey, I'm talking about Pooky, not my ears!
301840.mission_complete: Mission complete! Commander, don't forget about the rewards!
301840.main: "The invincible Suzutsuki is here! Your attacks shall not put a scratch on me!" How'd that sound? Hya hah!|Ahaha! You'd rather sit atop Commander's head instead of mine? 301840.upgrade: Give me more power, so that I may protect everyone!
301840.unlock: Ahaha, Pooky, listen up, we're gonna live here from now on! Uhh... Third ship of the Akizuki-class, Suzutsuki, reporting in! I'll be the one to protect my comrades and you, Commander! Just kidding~♪

301840.feeling1: Commander, you're gonna make me hate you...
301840.propose: Ahahaha... Being in a situation like this is quite nerve-racking, isn't it? ...I thought I had mentally prepared myself... Commander, you c-can handle the rest... right...?

Not a shabby record, right? I had a close call at the Battle of Bou-no-Misaki when I got hit by two torpedoes, but I managed to survive until the end!
301840.touch2: C-Commander! Jeez, there are some things that you shouldn't be doing!
301840.mission: A tough mission, huh? Lemme take a look, maybe I can help out!

couple_encourage: Be careful out there!
I will be the one to protect my friends!
Isokaze, back me up!

705010.feeling4: Ahahahaha! Well done, comrade! No matter how strong the enemies we may face, we now join each other courageously, prepared to give everything in pursuit of greater challenges! What could be more revolutionary than that?
705010.feeling1: There is no future for those who mistake recklessness with courage, comrade.
705010.propose: A pledge, huh? While this act is symbolic in nature, it is also undeniable proof of the bonds we've formed. A toast, comrade. Please continue to guide me in the future.
705010.profile: I am Gangut, a dreadnought from the Northern Parliament. My equipment may be outdated, but don't underestimate me. Both humans and ships are alike in their quest for greater power, to protect what they otherwise would not be able to. That is революция, the revolution I strive for! From the Bering Sea to Leningrad, only by rising up in the face of humiliation was I able to become a beacon for the light of glory!
705010.touch2: What are you doing, comrade? Are you not aware of how we handle lawbreakers in the Northern Parliament?
705010.mission: Missions exist for the sake of preserving the order. We should complete them as soon as possible.
705010.home: O comrade, do you return bearing news of glorious victory? Ah, but it matters not, for the thing that matters most is that you fought with all your strength!
705010.win_mvp: Rejoice, for we have earned this privilege! May this celebration become the bread that sustains us until our next victory!
705010.expedition: Hopefully our comrades will return bearing good news, unlike that bitter Ice Cruise. Come on, let's go welcome them back.
couple_encourage: Ahahaha! Finally, I have the privilege of fighting by your side, Mikasa!
For the light of revolution!
705010.mail: You have a letter, comrade. It would be best to open it soon.
705010.feeling3: I hope you don't take this the wrong way, comrade, but this fight is not just for all of us. It's also yours. Never settle with the status quo, and always seek to keep improving.
705010.lose: Comrade, consider this not a defeat, but rather a warning. A sign that we are losing sight of our revolutionary spirit.

Repair ship {namecode:98}

312010.lose: Nyooo~! Just wait until next time!

206030.unlock: I... I am... The Royal Navy's... Unicorn. ...Commander, can... can I call you... big brother?

206030.propose: This... precious thing... Are you really giving it to me? I, Unicorn... will work hard... That's because... I like big brother a lot!
206030.drop_descrip: Aircraft carrier – Unicorn, Hull Number I72!
206030.profile: Royal Navy's... support carrier... I am Unicorn... I was born to support my big sister Illustrious... Later, I went to support other big sisters... but everyone treated me nicely. I worked hard in lots of different ways, you know? ...It would be nice if I become a little dependable... Ehehe, I'll work harder, big brother

Unicorn loves singing... but singing in front of everyone else...///

408041.unlock: It's me, U-556, all prettied up! Eheheheh, we're gonna have lots of fun at this party, Commander! Come on, let's go!
408041.drop_descrip: It's me, U-556, all prettied up! Eheheheh, we're gonna have lots of fun at this party, Commander! Come on, let's go!

206010.detail: Statistics aren't important, it's how you take advantage of them.
206010.login: You're back. Now it's time to duel!
206010.battle: If you believe in your fleet, we'll work our hardest to meet your expectations!

206010.feeling5: If two duelists fall in love, Commander, they can undertake more duels together! They also must truly understand each other... I think that requirement is already fulfilled for us... so... shall we try?
206010.upgrade: The new me now can move to even greater heights with my deck!
206010.unlock: Glory to the cards, my soul to the duel d... I mean, the flight deck! I am Hermes. Commander, give me your orders!
206010.feeling4: Mmm... Commander, I decided to engrave your portrait on the back of my cards. That way you're always with me!

206010.propose: This feeling is……! The bonds formed between Commander and I here shall open up a brand new future, a path of brilliance! It’s our turn, draw!

I am called Hermes, I was the second aircraft carrier to be ever built.

206010.mail: You've got new mail, Commander. I wonder if it's a request for a duel!
206010.feeling3: Interests in anything besides dueling? Hmm... I've never thought about it. Will you show me something new, Commander?

205073.drop_descrip: My beautiful Adonis, why dost thou refuseth to take refuge in the trove of everlasting love... Perhaps my outfit can finally pierce thy heart? Hehe~

408040.home: Commander, I took out a whole bunch of books while you were gone and I kiiinda forgot where they go... Erm, sorry... Eheheheh...
408040.expedition: The girls are back from commission! Should we go greet them?
couple_encourage: Lord Bismarck! Let's give the enemy a beautiful thrashing!
Sorry, I don't really want to be around you...
Tirpitz! Watch this!
408040.mail: Beepbeepbeep! U-556 has received new information!
408040.feeling3: Commander, you wanna see how I dive? Heh heh, Lord Bismarck said it looked pretty good. I'm proud of myself too.
408040.lose: I won't fail like I did before... never again!

905010.detail: If some dumbass sticks their nose where it doesn't belong, they got only themselves to blame when they're hanging from my cannons.
905010.touch: Stop trying to hit on me.

905010.battle: Don't bother with courtesy! Just bunch up and come at me!
905010.feeling2: Your smile makes me think of her... She's someone I wanna hate, but can't bring myself to.

905010.upgrade: Feeling great. Wanna give it a shot?

905010.feeling4: I can't stand hearing those babies cry when you get hurt... So use me as a shield. I don't mind.
905010.feeling1: Seems you've mistaken a wolf for a dog... Hmph, don't start crying if you get bit cause of it.

905010.touch2: ... You better not regret this later.

905010.home: You finished plundering? Coulda gotten it done in no time if you'd brought me.

905010.expedition: Guess your rackety team's come back.
couple_encourage: That's enough praying. Prepare to fight!
You're not gettin' ahead of me a second time!
905010.mail: Got some mail for ya. Picked it up on the way here.
905010.feeling3: Stop looking so intimidated. Long as you won't betray me, I won't betray you.
905010.lose: My payback comes with interest... Before long, you'll know how much!

205061.detail: Regardless of the time and situation, to ignore a fair maiden is most ungentlemanly.
205061.touch: {namecode:79} looked pretty depressed after she lost the ball game... Commander, why don't you go and comfort her?
205061.login: To  truly experience the charm of all things, first one must sincerely love them. Commander, the same goes for girls too.
205061.mission_complete: Good work, Commander! How about a massage? People tell me I've got the best technique.

205061.feeling5: Love with you is like priceless treasure. I wouldn't trade even an entire kingdom for it!
205061.upgrade: I can't die happy until I see Prinz Eugen with a true and honest smile on her face.
205061.unlock: Although I don't really want in on the beachball game, but it was a request from Hood....That sun-loving girl. Don't forget to cheer for me!
205061.drop_descrip: I'm not a big fan of beach volleyball, but Hood begged me... I swear, that girl! She just can't get enough of the sun! You've got to cheer for me!
205061.touch2: Do you need me to teach you how to properly treat girls?
205061.mission: Fear not for dangers and obstacles, leap over challenges, and charge towards your goals. This is how unprecedented accomplishments are achieved!
205061.home: I know it's tempting to eat ice cream during the summer, Commander, but don't eat too much otherwise you'll get a stomachache!
205061.expedition: I'll welcome the girls home from commission. Take a rest if you're really tired.
205061.mail: New mail? Hood, stop staring at me. They aren't for me!

205060.detail: Fate can be easily derailed, Commander.
205060.login: Welcome back. Shall we have tea before getting back to work?
205060.battle: Courage is necessary for success… All ships, fire!
205060.hp_warning: Get up! We're going to go look for a fight!
205060.feeling2: I heard that my current name was chosen because my original one could bring misfortune, but... judging by how things turned out... it seems I'm unable to escape my fate...
205060.main: Expensive isn't always better, but it's your job to maximize our combat capability, Commander.|I don't want to suffer the pain of losing my comrades again...|Would you like to have some tea? I have also prepared some sandwiches. By the way, I am a fan of pickles.
205060.feeling5: I had a dream, a dream of that time which makes me feel hopeless even now... But when I open my eyes and see you by my side, it feels like life... like life isn't so bad after all...
205060.unlock: You're the Commander? Very well. I, Prince of Wales, shall let you witness my true strength.
205060.feeling4: Fighting fair and square is my motto. I wish it could be the same when it comes to my own feelings. So... can you stay with me a bit longer? I have something important to tell you, Commander...
205060.feeling1: Keep your distance. You are not qualified to command me...
205060.propose: To me, the ritual isn't as important as the fact that you're the person that I've accepted... However, receiving something like this still makes me happy. Thank you, Commander... I'll keep this with me forever!
205060.drop_descrip: King George V-class battleship – Prince of Wales, Hull Number 53!

205060.touch2: You know what doing this means right? *Smiles*
205060.mission: Commander, it's time to put you to the test.
205060.home: Sometimes victories come down to nothing but luck. Don't get too full of yourself, Commander.
205060.win_mvp: The taste of victory is always sweet.
205060.expedition: The commissions are complete, it is your duty to welcome them back.
couple_encourage: To be honest, I never know what you're thinking.
It is my honor to serve you, Your Majesty.
Hehe, shall we display the elegance of the Royal Navy?
If it's about the Commander, perhaps... we can talk about it.
Little Miss Vampire, what can I do for you?
Repulse, though this might sound quaint coming from me, you should try to concentrate a little more.
205060.mail: You have a new message, Commander.
205060.feeling3: You never know how many plans, hopes, and efforts would sink into the sea with you, Commander. So try not to die too easily.
205060.lose: A horse may stumble even though he has four legs. Let's try again next time.

205051.detail: Hmm...? These clothes seem a bit too tight. Commander, mind helping me loosen up the zipper in the back?
205051.touch: It seems... that Belfast and Hood are already attending to Her Majesty. Looks like we'll be free to enjoy ourselves, Commander.
205051.login: Take my hand, Commander. I'm still not used to walking around in this dress.

205051.main: Ugh... I'm expected to act more proper when I'm wearing formal attire. 205051.drop_descrip: Sorry to keep you waiting, Commander... I don't get to wear a dress very often, so it took me a bit longer. Let's get going, then. Remember, you'll be the lead tonight. Haha~

205050.login: Commander, did you already partake of supper?

205050.mission_complete: Supper tastes best after the day's missions are all complete. Wouldn't you agree, Commander?
205050.main: Commander, this fleet only functions because of you. Don't get sloppy on us. |Wales and Yorkie? It's a bit of a shame that they don't act more like cute little sisters, but I am glad that they have strong personalities. |In my eyes, there is no leader in this world more worthy of my loyalty than Her Majesty, Queen Elizabeth. 205050.feeling5: My greatest hobbies in life are food and fighting. While I am more than capable of fighting alone, dining by myself is quite difficult and lonesome. To be able to find someone who can share both of these things with me is truly a joyous thing.
205050.upgrade: Hmm... I suddenly feel like having a lavish feast.
205050.unlock: So this is my new battlefield. Ahh, how I've long awaited this... By the way, are you my commander? You are in the presence of King George V – do use me well.
205050.feeling4: Commander, so you're learning how to cook? Hmm, colour me impressed. I look forward to trying the dish that you're making for me.
205050.feeling1: I favor those of character, and those who can cook. Commander, you are neither.
205050.propose: They say that "the quickest way to one's heart is through their stomach," but you've managed to win over both at once. Commander, shall we share all our meals together from now on?
205050.drop_descrip: King George V-class battleship – King George V.
205050.skill: The glory of the sun that never sets shall not fade!
205050.profile: The nameship of the King George V-class battleships is none other than me. I served as flagship for my country, leading the fleet into numerous battles including the fateful encounter with Bismarck. After getting a brief taste of that thrill, I have been craving to cross swords with her once again... But I digress - is there anything else you'd like to know about me?
205050.touch2: Ohh? I wasn't aware that you possessed such audacity, Commander.
205050.mission: New missions, eh? It would be ideal if we got something a bit more challenging.
205050.home: Commander, did you thoroughly enjoy the battle?
205050.win_mvp: Make no mistakes. I shall ensure both victory and the safety of all my comrades.
205050.expedition: There's some commotion by the port...? Oh, it seems to just be the commission team returning.
couple_encourage: Wales, you'd better not suddenly leave me again!
York, let us shatter our enemies together.
205050.mail: A letter, huh? Now then, is this a challenge, or a love letter?
205050.feeling3: How's that, commander? Are you impressed by my cooking abilities? Here, have as much you desire. Seeing you enjoy my food pleases me.
205050.lose: Do not be demoralized. Neither victory nor defeat are decided by a single battle.

205048.detail: I have paperwork, practice, and dinner to see to today. The more burdens I can take off your mind, the happier it makes me~

205048.feeling5: Care to have dinner with me tonight, Commander? I know all your favourite dishes~

205048.drop_descrip: I never imagined that this dreamlike situation would come to pass... Commander, have you also been looking forward to sharing this moment with me? Hehe~
205048.touch2: Please, let's put this on hold until we're alone, all right?
205048.home: Well strategised, Commander. Wait just a minute while I go brew some tea.

107222.drop_descrip: Hmm... Isn't this one a bit too garish? Mm... What if we pair it with a necklace or some sort of purse? ...Commander, your thoughts? C'mon, don't just stare at me, give me something to work with here...

301055.drop_descrip: "Welcome, Commander..." I should greet customers like this... yes?

203030.feeling1: I'm disappointed... We don't make a good team at all.
203030.propose: Oh wow! Thanks, Commander! But something this important needs to be kept in a safe place. I can't afford to lose it.....

201290.skill: Here I come! Witness Echo's might!

201290.touch2: Wha...? Hood said I shouldn't let people touch me there...

201290.expedition: The commission girls are back~♪ Echo will go check if they brought any yummy snacks with them~
201290.mail: Mail has arrived~♪ Maybe there are yummy snacks enclosed within it~ Ehehe~
201290.feeling3: Commander, you can't give up so easily. You must get into shape~ Come on, take a stroll around the port with Echo~♪

You still don't have what it takes to be entrusted with important tasks... Keep honing your skills.
205030.feeling5: Go out on a date? Well... It's not as if I won't, as long as you keep on working hard then...
205030.upgrade: I suppose I should show a little appreciation for you; nice work.

205030.feeling1: I... don't even know what to tell you anymore... *Sigh*...
205030.propose: Stand straight and puff your chest. You are the one I have chosen to spend the rest of my life with. This is something you should be proud of! ... Of course, to be chosen by you, is my honor... I'm not arrogant anymore? ... W-why, you... Do you want me to beat you up that badly?!
205030.skill: You're making a big mistake if you think I'm going to underestimate our enemies!
205030.profile: If you don't know who I am, go back to the naval academy and start over. I have no need of a commander who doesn't know me. ... You're calling me slow?! Huh?! That's brave of you to say... Stand still, I'll launch some knowledge into your head with my cannons!
205030.touch2: Off to the bottom of Trafalgar with you, Com-man-der!
205030.mission: Why are you daydreaming if there are still missions to complete?
205030.home: Have you witnessed the might of the Royal Navy?
205030.win_mvp: Hmph. Enemies like these aren't even worth the time.
205030.expedition: Com-man-der! Did you forget about the returning commissions again?
couple_encourage: Renown, try not to ruin my reputation!
Your Majesty, please let me take care of this for you.
Akatsuki team, unleash your full firepower!
205030.mail: I picked up your mail while I was out on my walk. Read it and be thankful.
205030.feeling3: Just with results like these you want me to... You did all this yourself? Don't laugh! I suppose I can make an exception and admit that you did well this time. Hmph!
205030.lose: To humiliate me like this... I'll get you back!

101279.detail: Cutie, Lucky, I'm leaving the equipment to you two~!

101279.win_mvp: It's Bailey from Planet Bunny! Everyone, please give me your support~

Eh? Wouldn't that make me seem suspicious?
205021.feeling5: Apologies, Commander, it seems like our Christmas together was a bit unromantic. You... enjoyed it just fine? Heh, you're always like this... Well, at least, let us enjoy the rest of the night together while the bells of the Holy Night toll.

205021.drop_descrip: This year, I am in charge of delivering presents to the children of the Royal Navy. Let's get going once I finish decorating this Christmas tree!

103080.detail: Heyyo~ Commander, you look awfully bored~
103080.login: Commander, you can totally rely on me more!
103080.battle: I won't let you harm the people who are important to me!
103080.feeling2: I'm not as nice as you take me for...
103080.mission_complete: Here, the rewards have arrived~ Commander, you're pretty awesome~

103080.feeling5: Love is equal? ... Ehehe, you're always thinking about me, that makes me very happy~ However, here's what you don't understand: if you truly like someone, then these kinds of things don't matter at all.
103080.unlock: Yo, Commander! I'm Astoria, eldest sister of the New Orleans-class! If you're ever having any troubles, you can always come talk to me~
103080.feeling4: But, I'm totally over it. I've found something even more important than being a big sister... *sparkles* Commander, rely on me more and more, okay~
103080.feeling1: I'm getting a little pissed off... I know I said you can rely on me more, but...
103080.propose: Commander, just being able to exert myself for your sake is enough to make me happy, but for you to reciprocate my feelings like this... This is truly the greatest treasure I could ask for. Thank you.
103080.drop_descrip: New Orleans-class heavy cruiser – Astoria, hull number CA-34.
103080.skill: Even I can get serious when it's do or die!
103080.profile: Heyyo! I'm Astoria, the eldest sister of the New Orleans class! Why am I not the nameship? Um... it's kind of a long story, hehe... But that doesn't make me any less of a big sister. Commander, you can rely on me, that is if you want to~
103080.touch2: Ah... wait... Jeez, Commander, you jerk!

103080.home: Commander, you made it back without a scratch on you! Well done, well done!
103080.win_mvp: Hehe, I'm pretty capable, aren't I~

103080.mail: There's new mail~ Comander, you're quite the popular one~
103080.feeling3: I get along with my sisters very well, and like them a whole lot... But sometimes, I just can't help thinking... what if we were called the Astoria-class instead...
103080.lose: Oh my, looks like we lost... Commander, let's get out of here~

205020.detail: Don't be blinded by statistics. Victory depends on far more!
205020.touch: Body contact...? I don't hate it...
205020.login: As long as I'm here, we can deal with any enemy, no matter how far they are.
205020.battle: I would never let the commander's enemies escape!
205020.hp_warning: So this is how harsh the battlefield can be.
205020.feeling2: Commander, want to hear about the history of the Royal Navy? Maybe I should tell you something about the generals who used to accompany me.
205020.mission_complete: Missions give out rewards once you complete them. Don't forget that!

205020.feeling1: Would you please not act like we're close...
205020.propose: Finally the day has come! It looks like my efforts were not in vain... Let's go, Commander, I'm prepared for this. Officers, draw swords!
205020.drop_descrip: Queen Elizabeth-class battleship - Warspite, Hull Number 03!
205020.profile: Elizabeth-class fast battleship, Warspite, reporting in. I hold the record for the longest ranged hit on a moving target. I've come close to being defeated quite a few times, but I managed to cheat death every time. This must be my fate.
205020.touch2: Just so you understand, I'm definitely not that sort of, erm...
205020.mission: Accept your new mission and then get ready to head out, Commander!
205020.home: Whew, not a bad fight. Let's rest for a while.
205020.win_mvp: Don't be confined by the so-called "limits". It is indeed possible to be unsinkable!
205020.expedition: Commissions? I suppose I do miss running around on errands... Let's go. We need to welcome back those hard workers!
couple_encourage: Do you want to race this old lady?
Unmatched by any? *Sigh*...
Elegance does not belong on the battlefield.
Your Majesty, please look forward to my performance in battle.
Youngsters, follow me.
Don't overdo it, alright?
205020.feeling3: I'm not very elegant? I'm sorry that I'm not like Hood or the others... No... I'm not talking about my body...
205020.lose: My damage control isn't functioning?! I've lost control of my steering wheel as well! Why now, at such a critical moment?!

205014.detail: "Be not enchanted by dreams of silver and gold. There are yet many ways to earn your coin." ...Well said, Warspite.
205014.touch: You have our permission to collect this New Year's gift!
205014.main: Servant, bright us some of that Dragon Empery tea! We wish to compare it with Edinburgh's black brew!|Heh heh, you doubt the wealth of a queen? Just you wait for the next Royal Banquet!|It seems different places have different customs for New Year's gifts, eh? Hmph, no matter. So long as you carry on as a good servant, we may reward you at any time!
205014.unlock: Did I hear that you're supposed to give out red envelopes during the Dragon Empery's New Year? This is a fine chance to display the magnanimity of the Queen of the Royal Navy! ...Don't just run off with your gift! Spread the word of my glory, my servant!
205014.drop_descrip: Did I hear that you're supposed to give out red envelopes during the Dragon Empery's New Year? This is a fine chance to display the magnanimity of the Queen of the Royal Navy! ...Don't just run off with your gift! Spread the word of my glory, my servant!
205014.touch2: Watch your hands, servant! I curse you to lose your wallet!
205014.home: You've done well. This red envelope is your reward!
205014.mail: You are to check your mail at once...! And I do not mean this red envelope!

205013.detail: Servant, do advise me on these "club activities." I have heard much commotion about "idols" or something like that...
205013.touch: Did you go buy candy from the student store? Heh, even a noble such as myself must learn the tastes of commoners.
205013.login: Your Queen has arrived! Do make way, my subjects!
205013.main: Bel, where's my cake...? Servant, take Neptune with you and make yourself useful!|Warspite, how fares the tea party plans with Nagato and the others? Have George and the knights deliver the invites to them!|"Field trip?" Let us make our way to Sardegna! Have Veneto regale us with the most exquisite banquet!
205013.unlock: Hehe, behold the new outfit that I had Akashi make for me! Impressive, no? Prostrate yourself before the elegant charm of my school uniform, servant~♪
205013.drop_descrip: Hehe, behold the new outfit that I had Akashi make for me! Impressive, no? Prostrate yourself before the elegant charm of my school uniform, servant~♪
205013.home: Mathematics, check. History, check... Physical Education? Pass! A noble like me playing basketball with commoners? Unthinkable!
205013.win_mvp: Ehehe, why it's only natural, of course! Nothing like that self-proclaimed "spiritual leader!"
205013.mail: Time to check my locker~♪ ...Hm, a note from Newcastle? Um... "Already cleaned for you." ...Oh, I see.

306059.detail: Don't look so sad... I'll keep growing. I'm sure of it!
306059.touch: Commander, do ye like my Shikigami? They ain't the bitin' type, I swear!
306059.main: Commander, gimme a chance to prove myself!|Why does everyone treat me like a kid when I'm already all grown up?|Grown-ups need to play, too! Won't you play with me, Com~man~der?
306059.unlock: Commander, how do I look now that I've grown up? Are ya fallin' in love with me already? Mhm, ye definitely are~
306059.drop_descrip: Commander, how do I look now that I've grown up? Are ya fallin' in love with me already? Mhm, ye definitely are~
306059.touch2: I feel like I've definitely matured some! Commander, what do ya think?

603011.detail: I might get sunburnt? Ah, you're right, I should be more careful... Commander, would you mind helping me apply the sunscreen?
603011.touch: If there's anything you want me to do, just speak up~ Don't be shy~
603011.login: Commander? Did you doze off to the sound of the waves just now? Ahah, don't worry~ There's plenty of time, so you should enjoy your nap~
603011.main: Commander, would you like to try this sundae? Here, say "ahh~" Very good, very good~ |Playing in the water seems like a lot of fun. Commander, shall we join them as well? |The rhythm of the waves is quite hypnotic... Commander, if you want to take a nap, just come lie down over here and let me take good care of you~
603011.unlock: The summer's scorching heat is alleviated by the ocean~ Commander, why don't you set aside your worries and... cut loose a bit~?
603011.drop_descrip: The summer's scorching heat is alleviated by the ocean~ Commander, why don't you set aside your worries and... cut loose a bit~?
603011.touch2: Being at the beach always makes people more easygoing... I suppose I'll forgive you today~
603011.home: It must have been difficult fighting in this heat~ Mmhmm, good job out there~

205012.touch: Encore? Heh heh. I could give you a few more!
205012.login: Hah hah! Spread the word, servant! Let all be dazzled by our splendour!
205012.mission_complete: I've included a favour in your rewards. Show me your gratitude!
205012.main: "Grovel before me, servant!" ...Hm? It feels a bit different from usual...?|Like so...? Is this cuter? Very good then, well done, Matchless. My servant will be blown away!|A maid idol...? What is it Bel and Gloucester have been teaching you?
205012.unlock: Now this is a stage worthy of our majesty! You are not to leave our sight, servant! Let your passions burn for me!
205012.drop_descrip: Now this is a stage worthy of our majesty! You are not to leave our sight, servant! Let your passions burn for me!
205012.touch2: Watch your hands, servant! Or it's the oubliette for you!
205012.mission: An offer for me? W- well, it is a Queen's duty to hear out the commoners...
205012.home: Fine work. As a reward, you may have this portrait of me. Keep it well!
205012.win_mvp: Valiant, spread word of our victory far and wide!

205010.detail: Peasant! Who permitted you to peak?! I-I have not prepared myself yet...
205010.touch: Please do not touch our noble body so casually
205010.login: Despicable, to have me wait on you for so long!
205010.battle: Witness the might of a super-dreadnought!
205010.hp_warning: Why are you spacing out?! Hurry! Get them!
205010.feeling2: Work hard for the great Elizabeth!
205010.mission_complete: Kneel before me and accept your mission rewards!
205010.main: Being petite is a noble characteristic, understand?|You're saying I bumped into you? That's because you didn't make way for the Queen!|Do not touch my belly, it's rude!
205010.feeling5: Hey, can't you just leave your work to your underlings? How can you be a proper consort if you aren't always by my side?! I-I would be so lonely...
205010.upgrade: I have no need to get any stronger! But... well, if you're going through to effort of doing it, then...
205010.unlock: Are you the commander? You are still 100,000 years too early to command me! Well, I shall be generous and give you a chance... From this day on, you will be one of my faithful servants!
205010.feeling4: H-hmph! You have been slightly exceeding in your duty, thus I will make an exception and promote you to captain of the Royal Guard! When I call for you, you will come hither immediately! Understood? Immediately! Swiftly! At maximum speed!
205010.feeling1: You useless servant! I will have you relieved of your post!
205010.propose: Finally you have arrived before me. Foolish servant! Just how long did you intend to make me wait?! ...But I acknowledge your endeavors. Come here, I am giving you permission to take my hand! Yes! From now on I will always be with you!
205010.drop_descrip: Queen Elizabeth-class battleship - Queen Elizabeth, Hull Number 00!
205010.profile: I am the super-dreadnought of the Royal Navy. Make sure to remember my name! My military achievements? I let my subjects take care of those kind of things. I simply need to watch them do their work!
205010.touch2: W-wait... You fool, what are you doing?! I-I'll sentence you to death!
205010.mission: Hurry and finish the mission! Do not skip your work!
205010.home: A fine display, I shall be benevolent and permit you to rest.
205010.win_mvp: Piece of cake! There are no mistakes in my actions!
205010.expedition: The subjects tasked with a commission have returned. Go at once and see if they brought me a tribute!
couple_encourage: Warspite! Hurry up and take care of these enemies!
Now this is the fleet I've been wishing for!
Warriors of the Royal Navy, fight for glory!
The Queen orders you to move! THAT... INCLUDES... YOU!
These oversized sisters... What an eyesore! ＞＜
205010.mail: I have no interest in the contents of your mail... Mmh...
205010.feeling3: I'm sitting here for just a moment because I like the mood! Don't start getting any strange ideas!
205010.lose: How despicable! To have brought shame to the great Elizabeth! You better remember this!

705050.detail: Is that you, Comrade Commander...? I'm afraid the office is a bit messy. But we must make sacrifices to achieve our goals.
705050.touch: You want to deepen our camaraderie? Very good, let us start by making a firm handshake part of our regular routine.
705050.login: Comrade Commander, you are late. You must not forget your proletarian values.
705050.battle: Commence bombardment! We will bury them!
705050.feeling2: Your fleet must be an iron curtain... Hm, it's a metaphorical expression... My meaning is that I hope to see this fleet stand united, just like our Northern Parliament.
705050.mission_complete: Hm? Something missing from the reward manifest...? It should be generally correct...
705050.main: A report I submitted went missing? Pardon my negligence. I'll make it up, so... please don't tell the others about this matter. |I hope that you can command from a global perspective. After all, the responsibility on your shoulders is much greater than just that of an individual. |When I was inspecting my rigging, I noticed a few more screws than last time... Hm, an unexpected "increase in resource allocation?" That's a good thing, right? |Your tactics are too conservative! As long as it has not been sunk, it can repaired, learned from, strengthened, and optimized... Continuing this cycle is the best way of fighting.
705050.feeling5: Gah, well done...! I have no choice but to place the pride of the Northern Parliament on the line and face defeat at the hands of Comrade Commander's charm offensive! Now then, Comrade Commander, you face the full power of my love offensive!
705050.upgrade: An excellent strengthening. The next one should be so good.
705050.unlock: I am called "Sovetskaya Rossiya," and as the mightiest of all the Northern Parliament's battleships, I am her ultimate weapon. I will press onward to eliminate all obstacles that stand between you and the Revolution.
705050.feeling4: Mm, this food is well made... Comrade Commander, thank you for serving me this meal, but I have to wonder, is this more than simple social etiquette? C- could you have some ulterior motive for this charm offensive?
705050.feeling1: This negative attitude is unacceptable. You must be forcibly reeducated.
705050.propose: So long as I draw breath, I labor to carry out my mission. Not only as a member of this fleet, but also in service of the bonds you have forged... This is not a product of rational thinking alone, but also a decision born of my subjective opinion.
705050.profile: I am Sovetskaya Rossiya, of Project 23. I was part of a strategic plan during the war, but for several reasons never came to be. I see though that I can prove my value here in this fleet with a series of decisive victories.
705050.mission: We have a mission. I will handle the clerical work. You must be clear to focus on your duties as a commander.
705050.home: Rest. And tell me now of what glorious victory you have won, or how you turn defeat to our advantage.
705050.win_mvp: Kill confirmed. You cannot stop the Northern Parliament... You cannot stop our righteous liberation!
705050.expedition: Military commissions? They are part of the logistical aspect of proper fleet management.
couple_encourage: This is no time to ponder the meaning of life. Just show us your strength!
Kirov, aid me!
705050.mail: Mail. Comrade Commander, you must read it quickly before the next one comes bringing another letter.
705050.feeling3: Comrade Commander, what is this? You wish to deepen your relationship with me as an individual, not a representative of the Northern Parliament? Well, such subjective decisions are acceptable.
705050.lose: Gah, how humiliating... to think a material defect would surface at a time like this...!

901120.detail: I didn't really want to do this, but I'll see this idol mission through. I will bring the elegance of the Iris to the world stage.
901120.touch: Thanks for always cheering me on~
901120.login: Good morning. What will today's lesson be?
901120.hp_warning: There's no way I could dance like Émile...!
901120.feeling2: I am the dazzling Iris idol, Le Malin— Now, provide me the most elegant of instructions!
901120.mission_complete: F-finally, that's taken care of... Now all that remains is the collect the reward, elegantly...
901120.main: An "idol" is something that people worship and exalt. As the word suggests, we mustn't do anything that would shorten that distance.|Jean Bart told me to just enjoy myself, but... the expectant gazes of Le Triomphant and Richelieu... it burns!|That little girl from the Royal Navy.. . Not only does she act all innocent, she also sings about "prayer." Hehe, as if I'd let her steal my thunder~
901120.feeling5: Commander, on my day off, promise you'll take me on a date? I mean, uhh, sorry, I'll just head back to... Huh? Really?! Yaay! I can't wait to loaf around together— Ah, ahem... First, this concert...!
901120.unlock: I am the Iris's shining sword, Le Malin. As the shimmering idol who chases the waves, may your souls be healed by my songs of prayer.
901120.feeling4: Haah, haah... How's that? My performance was pretty on-spot, wasn't it? If you think so, let me take a break already! All right, I'll be heading off! Or, uhh, if you could prepare some tasty snacks for me...
901120.feeling1: This... must be carte blanche to loaf around as much as I want...
901120.propose: The fact that I'm standing upon this shining stage right now is due to all the support from you and my friends. Now, place that ring upon my finger, and may our vow preserve this radiance forevermore!
901120.drop_descrip: I am the Iris's shining sword, Le Malin. As the shimmering idol who chases the waves, may your souls be healed by my songs of prayer.
901120.profile: I am the Le Fantasque-class destroyer, Le Malin, reporting for duty. Heheh... Just watch, I'll do an amazing job on this idol mission. J-just to be clear, it's not like I was looking forward to this!
901120.mission: We got a job offer... Hopefully we can take care of it quickly and efficiently...
901120.home: Good work out there. Would you like to enjoy a most elegant cup of tea?
901120.win_mvp: Long live the glory of the Iris! Rejoice! Weep!
901120.expedition: The commission fleet has returned... Phew! That means I get to chill!
couple_encourage: Please make the lyrics easier to understand!
Let's do our best onstage!
You know... it really does feel better to just enjoy myself!
901120.mail: It's work-related. Look it over please.
901120.feeling3: Lessons, offers, training, and rehearsals... There's too much stuff to do... I can't deal with this anymore! I'm gonna pass out at this rate... Just looking at the schedule is making me want to crawl back into bed... Maybe I should do just that today~

204040.detail: There are many things that I do not understand in the Codex of the Royal Knights! Commander, can you offer me any guidance?
204040.touch: Candy? I'll have you know, Commander... Renown has no use for such things!
204040.login: Commander, Renown is awaiting your orders! Please issue today's commands!
204040.feeling2: I mustn't neglect my training or my studies... I'll do my utmost each day so that I may become a proper knight. Commander, do you want to follow this path as well?
204040.mission_complete: Heave-ho... C-Commander, the m-mission rewards are... wooooahhhh!!
204040.main: As long as Renown is here, no harm shall befall you, Commander! |The serious and dedicated Little Renown is cute? I see, I'll be sure to pass on the message to... wait, what? |It's not just you. Everyone here at port is truly amazing... I must redouble my efforts...!
204040.feeling5: So, Commander, is it fine for Renown to always stay here? Being close to you gives me strength, and above else, my love for you is absolute! ...Huh? Did I say something weird...?
204040.upgrade: For the Commander's sake, I'm ready... to become stronger!
204040.unlock: The Renown-class battlecruiser Renown has come to join your ranks! My stature may be small, but my desire to succeed is great!
204040.feeling4: Commander, why did the knights in that book betray their own king? Renown is nothing like those knights! I would never betray you even if it cost me my life!
204040.feeling1: Commander, please get your act together! Renown shall not abandon you!
204040.propose: A promise ring? I know about this! Um, "I pledge to defend the weak and act with valor..." Oh, all I have to do is read this? Well then... "through thick and thin, we shall share our pain and willingly give love eternal." ...Commander, does that sound right?
204040.skill: The enemy shall never see my back turned!
204040.profile: I am the battlecruiser Renown, and I was training in Govan before coming here! Being able to weigh anchor ahead of schedule is a testament to my strength... Indeed! I will do my utmost to live up to everyone's expectations!
