204040.touch2: Commander! That's in violation of Royal etiquette!
204040.mission: Commander, please allow Renown to handle the missions! H-huh? Commander, you're doing them all yourself?!
204040.home: You're not too bad, Commander... If Renown also works harder, will she be able to... be like you one day?
204040.win_mvp: I've done it...! Wait, no! The books clearly teach that it is foolish to gloat over a single victory! Self control... self control...!
204040.expedition: Commander! The commission fleet will return to port in ten minutes! Please... Wait, did I get the time wrong...?
204040.mail: This one's for you, Commander. This one's also for you... and this one too...
204040.feeling3: Work is important, but taking breaks is also important! Coming from a Royal Knight, you're overworking yourself! After you finish this, please make sure to get some rest!

502024.detail: Ping Hai can get away with it, but I can't believe YOU don't have a clear schedule for this vacation, Commander... Forget it, I'll make you one!
502024.touch: It's so crowded over here... Listen, um, could you hold my hand? ... I mean, with me.
502024.battle: Stop interfering with our vacation, you scrapheaps!
502024.mission_complete: This one's really expensive... But we do need a souvenir to take back home... Fine, we'll buy it!
502024.main: Hmph. Sure, we got this vacation for free, but we can't squander our money... Ping Hai! Don't go off ordering food! You too, Commander!|I've vaguely felt it since way back, but the Sakura Empire and Dragon Empery are similar in a lot of ways. But also dissimilar in many ways, obviously. Those are what feel fresh.|nil
502024.feeling5: H-Huh? Hey! Why do *you* have my tourist magazine, Commander? The red circle on the shrine that "makes lovers get married"? L-Look, I only marked it because I wanted to check it out while we're here, that's all!
502024.unlock: Commander, what are you spacing out for? Over here! They say that you'll have good fortune if you give this thing a shake!
502024.drop_descrip: Commander, what are you spacing out for? Over here! They say that you'll have good fortune if you give this thing a shake!
502024.mission: We have to visit *all* the places I've outlined in my schedule, Commander. And don't you think about giving up already!
502024.home: You're late! We're going to the next tourist attraction right now!
502024.win_mvp: You're willing to go *any* lengths to anger me, aren't you?

202160.detail: What's up, Commander? Missed me, have you? Hah, alright, have a seat and I'll get you some tea.
202160.touch: Feeling lonely, Commander? I'm always here for you.
202160.login: Had supper yet, Commander? If not, I could cook you something up.
202160.hp_warning: It's like back in Crete... Sod that! I'm not letting that happen again!
202160.feeling2: All combat, all makeup, all the time, that's me!
202160.mission_complete: Mission rewards, hooray~! Done your job proper, I'd say, Commander.
202160.main: Jamaica? Ah, yeah, proper oddball, that girl~ But it's all good as long as she's having fun, innit?|What's up? You look knackered... Fancy a nap in my lap, maybe?|Hey, take a gander at this, Commander! Fancy what I've done with my hair? How about my nails?
202160.feeling5: Slow to catch on, aren't you~ Right, question! Could you believe there's a girl out there who's always talking about love with you, isn't afraid to undress before your eyes, and has grown quite fond of you?
202160.upgrade: I'll do my part on the battlefield all proper like, so you can rest easy, Commander.
202160.unlock: Heeey! Fiji's here~! Are you the Commander? Hmmm...? Pfft... Hahaha! You don't look too shabby! Nice seeing you, Com~man~der~♪
202160.feeling4: Oh, hey, Commander. I was just about to head out. Getting dressed right now, you see~ Ah, don't be shy, you can look~ Later, I wanna get a look at you, too~
202160.feeling1: You need something, Commander? I'm kind of unavailable, really.
202160.propose: Hey, is my makeup looking decent? What about my outfit? Reckon I look as pretty as it gets? ...Good~ I've never dressed for this occasion before, so I want to look as good as possible~
202160.profile: Name's Fiji, I'm pretty much the nameship of my class. Things I fancy include... What? Spare the details? Then, if you're asking about my service record, all I did was fight in the Battle of Crete. Pretty rubbish record, innit... ahaha. Just gonna have to live with it and work on it, you know?
202160.touch2: If you wanna know my three sizes, can't you just ask? I mean, if you do, I'll tell you~ Hahaha~♪
202160.mission: You can't just go leaving missions unfinished, Commander~ Let's go finish them. Remember: I'm right with you.
202160.home: What're you staring into space for? Is that your way of saying "I want a hug"?
202160.win_mvp: Just doing my part on the battlefield, really!
202160.expedition: Commission team's come back. Don't forget to go greet them! Or else you'll hurt their feelings.
202160.mail: Mail's here, Commander. I'll leave it here, so check it when you've got the time.
202160.feeling3: Oh yeah, anyone in the fleet you fancy? Want me to assist you with them? Come on now, don't get your knickers in a twist~ I can keep a secret~
202160.lose: Commander, take everyone with you and retreat! Leg it...!

205029.touch: Commander, if you have something to say, just come out and say it. I'm happy to listen.
205029.login: My range extends even farther. Commander, send me out to fight, won't you?
205029.main: It is my duty as your secretary ship to counsel you, Commander. I won't hesitate to speak my mind if you make a poor decision.|Survival is the key to becoming a stronger person.|Battle is the fire that feeds one's growth. And so I fight with all that I have, in every conflict.
205029.unlock: Warspite, retrofitting complete. Mm, I rather like this feeling of being rejuvenated... Now, Commander, let us make our way towards new battlegrounds!
205029.drop_descrip: Warspite, retrofitting complete. Mm, I rather like this feeling of being rejuvenated... Now, Commander, let us make our way towards new battlegrounds!
205029.touch2: My important parts haven't grown at all...? Seems like someone wants to taste my high-angle mounts...

201090.detail: From the way you are looking at me, you must be thinking of 'this and that' kind of stuff! What?... That's... I mean lewd... Wha!
201090.touch: That's like child's play. Eh? ...No more? W-well, I'm an adult as well... ahaha...
201090.login: Commander, whatcha doin? ...Ah... no... *ahem* --I didn't say anything!
201090.battle: Little chicks, you will not die an easy death! ... Th-That's so embarrassing!
201090.feeling2: There's no way someone like you would have friends, Commander...
201090.mission_complete: WIth this amount, it's a little insufficient-- Eeeeh?! Don't take it all away!
201090.main: If there's anything, just leave it to me! What? ...N-Nothing at all? --Ahaha... haha...|I am su~per strong. Small fries like that just run away when they see me!|Please take proper care of a cutie like me! Because... I-I'm cute... yes!
201090.feeling5: Commander, if I say bad things, then get angry with me, alright? If you're the one angry, I... what?... I'm precious, so you won't get angry at this extent? .... Ugh... you dummy...
201090.upgrade: With this, I'm growing closer to adulthood...!
201090.unlock: You're the Commander? You totally look like you've never fought before. I am C-class's Crescent, and I'm not a child! Despite how I look, I have a lot of experience. I'm not afraid of anything. No~thing at~ all~!
201090.feeling4: Commander, why are you so kind to a girl like me... Everytime I get nervous I say mean things... Everytime it happens, I feel that it's inexcusable... My chest feels like it's being ripped apart...
201090.feeling1: I'm even more adult than you are, Commander!
201090.propose: Are you really fine with a girl like me? Really? You can't take this back! It's too late if you regret this, you know? ... H-hmph! On account of how you chose me, I-I'm staying with you thankfully!
201090.drop_descrip: C-class destroyer ー Crescent, Hull Number H48!
201090.profile: I'm teh C-class destroyer Crescent. I was assigned to the Home Fleet just like my sisters, but I've been to Red Sea and Indian Ocean before. I'll give you a painful reminder if you look at me like I'm a child. Hmph!
201090.touch2: Ah... ugh... that spot...!! It's fine because I'm an adult?! D-don't treat me like an idiot!
201090.mission: Missions! There are missions! Geez, don't let other people remind you every time!
201090.home: You didn't bump into our own allies, did you, Commander?!
201090.win_mvp: I could've won faster without these people getting in the way! Eh? ...D-don't give me that look!
201090.expedition: Commander, the commission team has come back. I'm an adult as well, so won't you send me out next time?
201090.mail: Here, your mail. Haa... There's no way someone like you would get love letters... *side glance*
201090.feeling3: Commander... You know... I said mean stuff to you before... Well... T-that's right! I mean... ugh --It's nothing! Hmph!
201090.lose: You ally ships should've tried harder! Ah, I-I'm sorry! I let my emotions got the better of me...

303019.touch: Commander~! Want to take a nap together?
303019.login: Commander, did you have a good rest? Me? Umm... I slept very well.
303019.main: I might have changed, but I'm still the same Furutaka, Commander!|Ouch! Ah... I just bumped my head again...|My hair feels a bit messy... maybe Kako can teach me how to tie it up.
303019.unlock: What's wrong, Commander? Why are you staring at me like that? My body? Yes, some things seem to have gotten bigger... Want to take a look?
303019.drop_descrip: What's wrong, Commander? Why are you staring at me like that? My body? Yes, some things seem to have gotten bigger... Want to take a look?
303019.touch2: Since you like me so much... I suppose it's okay~
303019.expedition: It sure is nice weather, isn't it? I feel like taking a nap. Oh? The girls are back from commission~!
couple_encourage: Don't blame yourself, {namecode:55}! It's fine.

101020.detail: Is there something on your mind, Commander? Something you need my help for...?
101020.touch: My hair is a little messy? Oh, thank you for pointing it out! Please let me return the favor by giving you a massage later!
101020.login: Welcome back, Commander. Could we inspect the port's emergency relief supplies? You never know when disaster might strike.
101020.battle: I'll do the best I can for everyone's sake!
101020.hp_warning: I've taken significant damage... but I'm still in the fight!
101020.feeling2: Are you hungry, Commander? Then would you like me to cook some curry and rice for you? Just so you know, I can't guarantee you'll like it.
101020.mission_complete: Isn't it wasteful to simply leave the mission rewards sitting there?
101020.main: I love listening to music. My favorite song is made by Lexington!|Eep! S-Sorry, Commander! Typhoons and thunder are just too scary for me...|The caring Yorktown, the cool Enterprise, the peppy Saratoga... The Eagle Union has good people left and right.
101020.feeling5: Commander, does your freshly dried futon feel comfy? Keeping your living environment clean is good for your health. But I'll look after you if you should ever fall sick, so don't worry about that!
101020.upgrade: No matter how tough the going gets, I will not let anyone down!
101020.unlock: I'm Dewey, I'm a destroyer. If there's anything I can help with, please just say the word. Whatever I'm tasked with, I'll give it my all!
101020.feeling4: Did you lose something, Commander? Then I'll search your room and try to find it!
101020.feeling1: You're scarier than any storm, Commander...
101020.propose: Is this... for me? Am I really your most beloved...? Okay! I can't promise I'll be perfect, but I will support you in any way I can, be it at work or in private!
101020.drop_descrip: Farragut-class destroyer – Dewey, Hull Number DD-349.
101020.profile: I'm the Farragut-class destroyer, Dewey. I took part in many carrier convoys and support missions. I pride myself on my service history! Although... I sadly couldn't save two of my sister ships who were in trouble... Typhoons can be frighteningly strong...
101020.touch2: Hm...? My chest doesn't hurt, so why'd you do that?
101020.mission: If missions feel like a chore to you, let me take care of them!
101020.home: Well done on the last mission! Allow me to take care of the after-combat report, and you can get some rest in the meanwhile.
101020.win_mvp: I did only what was expected of me. Everyone else deserves the rewards!
101020.expedition: The commission team has returned! They've brought with them exactly what we needed, so let's put it to good use!
couple_encourage: Could we perform together again?
I'll keep you covered, Sara!
I never thought I'd get to fight with you again... I'll do my absolute best!
Gridley, just fire whenever you want.
101020.mail: Commander, please check your new intel regularly. By staying up-to-date, you can prevent disaster from striking.
101020.feeling3: Commander, I cleaned your office earlier. Wouldn't you say it looks more orderly now? I could clean your bedroom too, if you'd like!

201218.detail: By the way, Commander, I just remembered how I was making a goofy grin the whole time at our ceremony... Sorry, but I just couldn't help it! At that time, I just felt way too happy!
201218.touch: Hup! ... Hehe, being in Commander's arms is the most comfortable of all~
201218.battle: I'll show you the power of love!
201218.mission_complete: Commander, make sure to collect the task reward! Please check when you have some time!
201218.main: Commander, even though I already know that you're always looking after me, I'll still get upset if you don't pay attention to me! |Commander, is there anything you'd like Javelin to do? Really? Nothing at all~? |Commander, it's all your fault! I walked into this wall because I couldn't stop daydreaming about you!
201218.feeling5: On the most important day of my life, I'm wearing the most beautiful wedding dress, and the ring given to me by most cherished person... For me, this is the greatest happiness I could ever experience, Commander~!
201218.unlock: Today, I must be the happiest girl in the world! Hehe~
201218.drop_descrip: Today, I must be the happiest girl in the world! Hehe~
201218.touch2: Ahhhn~! Ah, Commander... did I make a really "adult" sound just now?!
201218.mission: Commander, helping you complete your missions is simply the right thing for me to do, eheh!
201218.home: Commander, when you come back from battle, does seeing your cute little Javelin lift your spirits? Ehehe~
201218.win_mvp: Hehe, nothing can overcome the power of love!
201218.expedition: Commander, I'll come along with you to welcome everyone back~
201218.mail: Commander, I put the mail on your desk!

204030.detail: Feel free to admire the glory of the Royal Navy to your heart's content.
204030.touch: Appropriate contact is indeed essential. Shall we dance?
204030.login: Welcome back, Commander. Care for a cup of tea?
204030.battle: May glory be with us today.
204030.feeling2: Commander, it's such a great afternoon. Shall we have a chat? ... Hm, alright... I'll talk about the times when I was with Renown.
204030.mission_complete: With glory comes rewards. Please do not forget about the latter.
204030.main: An outstanding commander must have an in-depth knowledge of tea.|This word is... ah, so I read it wrong. Sorry, my eyes fail me.|Listen more, speak less. You should listen to the opinions of others, but also retain your own judgment.
204030.feeling5: "Shall I compare thee to a summer's day? Thou art more lovely and more temperate... So long as men can breathe, or eyes can see, so long lives this, and this gives life to thee." ... A beautiful verse. Commander, could you read it out loud to me?
204030.upgrade: Your efforts will definitely be rewarded.
204030.unlock: Are you the commander? Greetings and well met. I am the glory of the Royal Navy: Hood. Wherever I go, victory follows.
204030.feeling4: Hm? I'm too close? A lady must be elegant, but they must also seize the initiative towards the targets of their own affection.
204030.feeling1: *Sigh* Seems like you must learn it the hard way.
204030.propose: Aha, look how nervous you are. You can't convey your feelings to a lady when you're this nervous. However, your feelings have definitely reached my heart... I would happily oblige.
204030.skill: Elegance is not just for show.
204030.profile: Indeed, the glory of the Royal Navy now stands before you. Being able to maintain an air of elegance at all times is the hallmark of royalty. The Denmark straits? Soldiers know of victory and defeat alike. It was no more than a temporary setback.
204030.touch2: Commander, you should understand the consequences of disrespecting a lady... Are you prepared?
204030.mission: Commander, we have been entrusted with new missions. Please look through them.
204030.home: Commander, may I offer you some warm tea? We can drink it as we review your battle.
204030.win_mvp: The warm sun and the cool breeze: a brilliant victory.
204030.expedition: Having completed numerous commissions is a sign of glory. May I suggest rewarding those girls?
couple_encourage: Miss Renown, please mind where you're going.
Miss Repulse, mind your manners.
I shall do anything you ask of me, Your Majesty.
The glory of the royal family, advancing.
204030.mail: It's unopened... Commander... It would be ungentlemanly to ignore the messages of others.
204030.feeling3: Though I speak of being refined at all times, you need not force yourself, Commander. Your normal self is the most charming, after all.
204030.lose: Victory and defeat are commonplace among those who fight, and it is we that have all the time in the world!

204038.touch: Commander, let me teach you the proper etiquettes of being with a lady.
204038.login: Don't be so impatient, Commander. The boundless sea is rushing towards you with open arms.
204038.main: Which black tea did you prepare for us, Commander? Please allow me to build up my anticipation for this tea party. | Commander, once the seven seas have returned to peace, let’s organize another “Imperial Cruise”.
204038.drop_descrip: If the smooth path only allows one person to travel at a time, then I’ll gladly walk the path not taken with you hand-in-hand.
204038.touch2: There’s no need to be in such a rush... I’ll always be by your side.
204038.home: Commander, everytime I picture your face, my heart races and my spirit soars like a skylark at dawn.

306061.detail: It's good to always be ready for battle, but this isn't... so bad either, wouldn't you agree, Milord?
306061.touch: Zzzzz... Milord?! Are we being attacked?! ...I lowered my guard and fell asleep? Forgive me for this shameful display!
306061.login: *yawn*... O-one moment! I'll get myself in order!
306061.main: I cannot believe how addictive this technological marvel of a game console can be...! B-but that's not to say it has no merits whatsoever! After all, if we could settle wars through these games, nobody would have to get hurt!|nil|C-can we really allow foodstuffs as devilishly tempting as these deep-fried chips of potato to exist in our society?!
306061.feeling5: These games and snacks are a sort of trial for me! Rest assured, Milord! My devotion will not be swayed by the likes of these items!
306061.unlock: *yawn*... Finally, a good night's rest... Now, to pick up where I left off on that RPG... M-m-m-milord, why are you here?! I wasn't slacking off or anything, I w-w-was just... Ughh....
306061.drop_descrip: *yawn*... Finally, a good night's rest... Now, to pick up where I left off on that RPG... M-m-m-milord, why are you here?! I wasn't slacking off or anything, I w-w-was just... Ughh....
306061.home: Splendid work, Milord! If you so like, come take it easy with me!
306061.win_mvp: Milord! C-could you please consider rewarding me with some potato chips?

204010.detail: All systems functioning properly. Do not worry, Commander.
204010.touch: ... It's a bit strange... Only you have ever done this to me, Commander...
204010.login: Commander, please give me your orders.
204010.battle: Enemy fleet in sight! All ships, fire at will!
204010.feeling2: Love letter? How does one love something like a letter? People love all sorts of things, but that one I cannot understand.
204010.main: No instructions, Commander? So we're using the, 'wait and see' strategy...?|My propeller? Hood bumped into me one day, and before I reacted I received this in apology.|What? You think Renown is cute...? Well, on her behalf, I give you my tha... Wait, what?!
204010.feeling5: Don't worry, I'm not that dense. Next time I will bring a cap and cover up the candles for you. Then you can tell me what is truly on your mind.
204010.upgrade: Your will is the source of my power.
204010.unlock: Renown, Battlecruiser of the Royal Fleet of the Royal Navy, at your service. My guns shall aim where your sword points, Commander.
204010.feeling4: ... Why would you arrange candles in a heart on the beach? And then... why did you cry when I said "aren't you afraid of the fire being extinguished by the wind"?
204010.feeling1: Commander, you cannot continue like this.
204010.propose: Wait, Commander... Let... let me find some candles...and make a heart... and some covers to prevent them from being blown out.... t-t-then I'll... Please... don't look at me! I must be making a very strange face right now!
204010.profile: I am Renown, Battlecruiser of the Royal Fleet of the Royal Navy. I have experienced issues in both great wars, and have countless accomplishments for which I am proud. No matter what orders you give me, Commander, it is my duty to carry them out with all of my strength!
204010.touch2: ...!! Commander! I do not intend to resist... but still...
204010.mission: Commander, we still have missions to complete!
204010.home: I will review this operation's performance and report back to you as soon as I can.
204010.expedition: The girls who went out on a commission have arrived. Please, let me go in their stead next time, Commander. I... don't like being on the receiving end of things.
couple_encourage: It's an honor fighting with you!
Speed: 29 knots! Renown: attacking!
Renown: firing on enemies upon sight!
204010.mail: If you have time, please look over the mail.
204010.feeling3: Commander, you always ask me to accompany you for walks. Is something bothering you?
204010.lose: ...I am sorry, Commander... I failed to live up to your expectations.

203091.detail: London's complaining about how she doesn't want to wear her swimsuit again because it's "too revealing" ...*sigh*. She could probably benefit from learning to think more positively about herself, like Shropshire does.
203091.touch: Commander, are you also interested in surfing? Hehe, I'll teach you the basics.
203091.login: Commander, how's your work coming along? If I find out that you've snuck out here... Hehe~
203091.mission_complete: Did you buy this ice cream for me...? Th-thanks...
203091.main: People aren't changing into swimsuits just for your viewing pleasure... Got it? |You should watch yourself around Shropshire. That girl develops a variety of... how should I say this? ...Bad habits during the summer? |Hm? It's nothing. When we're at the beach, you can do whatever you want. *sigh*... It's just that... looking at your mug makes me really uneasy for some reason...
203091.unlock: What are you spacing out for? Have you not gotten tired of staring at all the swimsuits yet? Good grief... Are you able to help set up the parasol or the beach chairs at least?
203091.drop_descrip: What are you spacing out for? Have you not gotten tired of staring at all the swimsuits yet? Good grief... Are you able to help set up the parasol or the beach chairs at least?
203091.touch2: You just won't learn your lesson...!
203091.mission: A mission? I'll also come with you... That's my job as secretary after all!
203091.home: How many times have I already told you, Commander? Finish your missions first before taking time off.
203091.expedition: Commander, when you go welcome the commission fleet back, can you take this plate of ice-cold watermelon with you? It's a little courtesy from me.

303020.detail: If you want to say something, just give it to me straight!
303020.login: Good timing, I just finished sorting your documents. Can you actually finish these?
303020.battle: In any case, I shall set the standard for heavy cruisers!
303020.feeling2: I suppose I'll have to teach you how to behave in a respectable manner, Commander. Earning my acknowledgement is no easy feat, so I hope you've steeled yourself.
303020.mission_complete: So you can work hard as well, huh? Here are the rewards.
303020.main: This fleet is quite impressive, except for their commander.|You made a mistake here. And here. Do I have to tell you how to do everything?|I wonder how {namecode:55} is doing right now...
303020.feeling5: You've been learning quickly lately... About that... hm... If you want to experiment with me, I'm ready.
303020.upgrade: I suppose I should thank you for this.
303020.unlock: Second ship of the Furutaka-class, Kako, ready for orders. Why don't you show me whether you're worthy or not.
303020.feeling4: You still have a long way to go, but I suppose you're doing well for now... Just how long do you plan to cling to me anyway? How despicable... it seems like you haven't learned anything yet.
303020.feeling1: It seems that you'll never be able to earn my respect.
303020.propose: You've passed, but just barely! This is only the beginning... there's still a long way to go! What about me? If you want to spend the rest of your life with me, I'm ready!
303020.skill: Let me show my true strength!
303020.profile: Second ship of the {namecode:53}-class heavy cruisers, {namecode:54}! I was perhaps the first real heavy cruiser made for my country. Despite contributing to the first Battle of the Solomon Sea, I took too many risks and ended up being sunk by a submarine... My personality? I'm only like this when I'm around you. Open your eyes and learn the advantages of a real heavy cruiser!
303020.touch2: Why you little... Hello? Could I speak with the Military Police?
303020.mission: New missions, Commander. Surely you can handle these.
303020.home: Taking a break? Well... since you put in your fair share of work, why don't you set the rest of these files aside for later?
303020.win_mvp: To think that you could do this much... I suppose I can offer you a word of praise.
303020.expedition: The commission fleet has returned. Do you plan to sit here and wait for them to bring the resources to you?
303020.mail: Mail's here. I'm surprised you have so many friends.
303020.feeling3: To make this pose, put your hands here... What? You're embarrassed by me touching you? ...I'm blushing? Wh-what nonsense!
303020.lose: Tsk... Can't you work a bit harder?

203081.detail: York took a look at the roses earlier and went off about them being "Bloody Roses" or something. Just more of the usual, huh?
203081.touch: Eek! I almost got some wine on the dress!
203081.login: Sorry for the wait. Well then, let us head to the party. I, on behalf of the Royal Navy, would like to give you a warm welcome.
203081.main: I'd really like for my sister to stay silent around the others so as to not sully the glory and dignity of the Royal family, but...|The parties Her Highness hosts are always fantastic. Everything about them is just so perfect!|I can't stop worrying about the off chance that I'll spill some wine on this dress...
203081.unlock: Cheers, Commander. I'm glad that the party is a success. Well, I should take care as well to not sully the honour of the royal family with my actions.
203081.drop_descrip: Cheers, Commander. I'm glad that the party is a success. Well, I should take care as well to not sully the honour of the royal family with my actions.
203081.touch2: Aah! Don't surprise me like that! I ended up spilling some wine on my dress...
203081.home: The lovely smell of roses makes for a wonderful atmosphere. Please relax for a bit, Commander.

102220.detail: I set the trap just like the book said, but why haven't I caught anything yet? That's strange...
102220.touch: I know you're tired, Commander, but you don't have to whine about it. ... Okay, once you finish your work, how about I give you a massage?
102220.login: Clock's ticking! We gotta get to work— Oh, come on! Here, let me straighten your collar. You're a mess!
102220.battle: I'll keep the skies clear for you! Everyone, forward!
102220.hp_warning: I-it's just a scratch! I can keep going...!
102220.feeling2: The fleet is gonna lose faith in you if you keep spacing out like that. Commander, get your head in the game!
102220.mission_complete: Mission complete! Feels pretty nice to be done, huh?
102220.main: Commander... are you daydreaming again?|Supporting a carrier group is just watching the skies all day. I wish supporting you was as easy...|My sisters haven't been causing you any trouble, have they? Oh, thank goodness...
102220.feeling5: Um, I was thinking, if you have time, could we go out on a da... date? I know it's my fault for being so hard on you all the time, so I'm trying to make it up to you... Whatever I need to do to take us to the next level, I'll do it... Okay!?
102220.upgrade: Now I can escort those carriers even better!
102220.unlock: I am San Juan, Atlanta-class anti-aircraft cruiser number four. I've served as a support unit for the Eagle Union's carrier fleets. You seem like a person up to your ears in work, Commander... so I now offer to support you!
102220.feeling4: Commander, I always thought you wouldn't like me... and I'm glad that isn't true! B-but, how do we take our relationship to the next level? Wh-what are we supposed to do? I... I don't know about these things...
102220.feeling1: I thought this might happen, but... I won't give up!
102220.propose: L-look, Commander... I'm only doing this because you're easier to deal with than my sisters. I only have enough patience to take care of one more person, so thank your lucky stars that it's you! I wouldn't do this for anyone else, got it?!
102220.drop_descrip: Atlanta-class light cruiser – San Juan, Hull Number CL-54.
102220.profile: I am San Juan, Atlanta-class anti-aircraft cruiser number four. I escorted many carrier groups: Enterprise, Saratoga, several of the Essex-class. I fought alongside them all. Let's just say I have a lot of experience in aircraft carrier support combat!
102220.mission: How do you still have unfinished missions? Well, since you're hopeless without me, I suppose I can help you out...
102220.home: Welcome back, Commander! ... D-did it go okay?
102220.win_mvp: Victory is just a result of the effort we put into the fight. It's nothing to be especially proud of.
102220.expedition: The resources from the commission have been delivered. Commander, why don't you... Umm, I'll go check on them.
couple_encourage: You don't always have to put so much emphasis on the "sister" thing!
San Diego, quit screwing around already!
Juneau, you don't have to push yourself if it gets too scary out there...
102220.mail: I got your mail for you. Don't forget to check it.
102220.feeling3: Um, I know I can be a little hard on you, Commander. But you get what I mean, don't you? ... Commander?
102220.lose: Agh...! Go! I'll cover your retreat!

101271.detail: Cutie, Lucky, listen closely! Today's mission is to extract a whole bunch of candy from the commander!
101271.touch: Candy given away can never be reclaimed~!
101271.login: Trick or treat! If you don't hand over the candy, Baily and the Bunnykin will play a trick on you!
101271.main: Commander, your candy contribution will be distributed among the residents of Planet Bunny! Ehehe~☆|Don't you have any carrot candy? Bailey craves carrot candy!|Bailey's a black bunny today. Don't mistake it for a regular ol' white bunny!
101271.unlock: Can you see the ghost next to me? Hehehe— the black witch from Planet Bunny is none other than me, Bailey!
101271.drop_descrip: Can you see the ghost next to me? Hehehe— the black witch from Planet Bunny is none other than me, Bailey!
101271.touch2: This strange sensation... Could it be EM waves from Planet Bunny...?
101271.home: Bailey doesn't do pumpkin pie, but you can have this delicious carrot cake instead!

203080.detail: I'm counting on you for the inspection, Commander.
203080.touch: Even though I'm a member of the royal family... you still treat me as an equal, Commander. I'm touched.
203080.login: As a royal elite, I shall not disappoint you, Commander!
203080.battle: I swear upon the honour of the Crown that I, Exeter, shall fulfill my duties and my destiny!
203080.feeling2: Commander, don't be blinded by romance.
203080.mission_complete: Honours and rewards have been delivered.
203080.main: I can feel the honour of being in the Royal Navy no matter where I am!|York is talking nonsense yet again...|My skirt gets wet all the time... Should I change into something a bit more suitable for battle?
203080.feeling5: What's important is the present. If there is such a thing as fate in this world... I believe we were destined to meet.
203080.upgrade: For the honour of the royal family, I shall not be humiliated!
203080.unlock: Exeter, York-class heavy cruiser number two, reporting in! In the name of the Royal Navy, I swear that I shall contribute to your cause, Commander!
203080.feeling4: Commander... actually... I was thinking, if you were a normal person and not a commander, would I come to like you as well...?
203080.feeling1: Please do not bring shame upon the royal family.
203080.propose: For better for worse, for richer for poorer, in sickness and in health, to love and to cherish, till death us do part, according to God's holy ordinance; and there to I give thee my troth, Commander.
203080.drop_descrip: York-class heavy cruiser - Exeter, Hull Number 68!
203080.skill: For the glory of the royal family!
203080.profile: Exeter, York-class heavy cruiser number two, reporting in! I took part in chasing down Admiral Graf Spee. No matter how numerous the opposition, I shall never back down when fighting for the honour of the Royal Navy!
203080.touch2: ...!! T-this kind of... please, don't... As a member of the royal family... if someone saw us like this...
203080.mission: Please make sure to fulfill your duties - in the name of the Crown!
203080.home: Exeter has returned to port! I will prepare the after-action reports right away!
203080.win_mvp: I am the successor of a long line of royals, and shall embrace my destiny with countless victories to come!
203080.expedition: The girls who went out on a commissions have returned. It is my duty to at least receive them properly, Commander.
couple_encourage: My sister, let us fight for glory!
203080.mail: Mail for you, Commander. I hope it is good news!
203080.feeling3: Living with the royal family means I cannot decide my own fate. It is great to have met someone as excellent as you, Commander.
203080.lose: Curses... I shall have my revenge!

306060.detail: Milord, we cannot survive unless we fight!
306060.touch: Milord, please be careful. I am just as top-heavy as Illustrious.
306060.login: A day off? Milord, my week only consists of Monday, Monday, Tuesday, Wednesday, Thursday, Friday, and Friday!
306060.feeling2: Milord, when it comes to war, victory is more important than good or evil!
306060.mission_complete: The mission rewards are here! A bagel? Is this a snack for me? Thank you, Milord. Well then, let's move out!
306060.main: Odango... these delicacies will cause my heart to waver, so... Um, I suppose I can reward myself a little.... Mmmh! So delicious! |When you're stressed out, you should go watch the fish swimming around peacefully in the aquarium. I'm not sure why, but it always calms me down. |I fight for a just cause! No matter who stands before me, I swear to give it my all!
306060.feeling5: Just being able to see your face before I sortie fills me to the brim with energy and makes me feel like I can't lose to anyone!
306060.upgrade: Thank you very much, Milord! Shall we go run a lap to test my new strength?
306060.unlock: Milord, I am called Ryuujou, a ranger from the Land of the Rising Sun! I shall lay down my seven lives to mete out justice in your name!
306060.feeling4: Commander, did you prepare this meal for me by yourself? In that case, I'll be more than glad to dig in! Mm... thanks for the food! Eh? You'll continue to cook for me when I come back!?
306060.feeling1: No matter where you are, the top brass is all the same...
306060.propose: From now on, no matter what perils we might face, I will protect you with everything I have! Even if I sink to the bottom of the ocean, I will not permit any harm to come to you!
306060.skill: As long as I am here, nothing shall stand in my way!
306060.profile: I am Ryuujou of the Sakura Empire, a seasoned warrior who has served in the First through Fourth Carrier Divisions, and participated in campaigns in the Phillipines, East Indies, Aleutian Islands, and Guadalcanal. I don't look the part...? Th-that must be because of that one incident at Iwate that stunted my growth! Milord, just you wait. I'll show you the extent of my capabilities!
306060.touch2: Eek!!! Oh, it wasn't Saratoga after all. However, you seem to be even more mischievous than she is.
306060.mission: A new mission is here! Whether it's combat or training, let's knock it out at the speed of sound!
306060.home: Don't break formation even when we head back to port! The glory of the Sakura Empire is in its meticulousness!
306060.win_mvp: Despair... shall be your final destination!
306060.expedition: Worldly things are of little significance! The only things that matter are spirit and resilience!
306060.mail: A telegram? Oh, it's not a combat report from Headquarters. I suppose there might be some value to reading it then.
306060.feeling3: Commander, feel free to rely on me as you please. Should you will it, I will execute any command.
306060.lose: Ugh... my body is all beat up...

602010.detail: I am the final development from a class of treaty cruiser. With the performance enhancements I recieved, victory is but guaranteed in any battle I partake in.
602010.touch: What do you need, Commander? I can perform some of your duties in an official capacity.
602010.login: Greetings, Commander. The Empire's splendor radiates as brightly as ever.
602010.battle: To battle! My splendor shall be proven!
602010.hp_warning: As long as I can still fight, I will!
602010.feeling2: My name is Luigi di Savoia Duca degli Abruzzi. You find that too hard to memorize? Then you may shorten it to Duca degli Abruzzi, but no less than that. My dignity won't allow it.
602010.mission_complete: Mission complete. It's time you looked over the rewards.
602010.main: How can you sit idly like this, Commander? We dignitaries must set an example for others to follow.|It matters not how strong your adversary is as long as you are stronger. That is what war boils down to.|Hmm. Climb Mount Niitaka? I see I'm not alone in the desire to mountaineer... What? That's not what the message means?
602010.feeling5: What do you want to discuss today, Commander? One cannot do much without the aid of loyal supporters, and I strive to be your biggest one. Hahah. It's the least I can do to return the recognition you've given me.
602010.upgrade: Now the question is, how to make the best use of my new abilities?
602010.unlock: I am light cruiser Luigi di Savoia Duca degli Abruzzi, Sardegna's splendorous dignitary. I've waited for the day to fight under your banner, Commander.
602010.feeling4: I am not just a soldier at your disposal, Commander. I am someone with a desire to understand and support you to my utmost. This desire has nothing to do with rank or status.
602010.feeling1: You've proven yourself a spineless imbecile. Get out of my sight!
602010.propose: This ring could only mean one thing. You want my support till death do us apart, no? Then I will oblige. After all, there is no greater joy than knowing you want me by your side forever. Hahaha.
602010.drop_descrip: Duca degli Abruzzi-class light cruiser – Luigi di Savoia Duca degli Abruzzi.
602010.profile: I am the Condottieri-class light cruiser Luigi di Savoia Duca degli Abruzzi, from the Sardegna Empire. I fought valiantly alongside my esteemed allies during the war. My ambition now is to achieve lustrous feats as the Empire's splendorous flagbearer!
602010.mission: Say the word, and I will complete these missions for you.
602010.home: If you need rest, now is the time to get it, Commander. We will have much to do afterwards.
602010.win_mvp: I am the Empire's splendor – Duca degli Abruzzi! Etch this name into your memories!
602010.expedition: The commission team has returned to port. It is part of your job to acknowledge their efforts, is it not, Commander?
602010.mail: You have a letter. Whoever wrote it is brutishly uncourteous... It's what? From Naval HQ? I see.
602010.feeling3: Don't fret over each and every obstacle you face, Commaner. Your subordinates will do all in their power to help.
602010.lose: Alas, we must shamefully turn our backs on our foes...

302090.detail: Don't push yourself too much, Commander!
302090.login: Welcome back. Want to try some fresh torpedoes?
302090.hp_warning: Don't panic... wait for the right moment to strike!
302090.feeling2: What's wrong? If it's nothing then stay quiet, Commander.
302090.main: Commander, shall we go fishing? How about a game of chess?|My name seems a bit complicated, but it's actually easy to read. Why don't you try it?|Dress up? Oh... these socks are actually pretty easy to take off. Want to try yourself?
302090.feeling5: I'm just a normal {namecode:47}... no one has ever cursed me to become a demon. If someone tries to hurt you though, Commander, I might just turn right into a demon!
302090.upgrade: This isn't a bad feeling at all...
302090.unlock: Hi, Commander... I'm {namecode:47}. What are you looking at? My horns? Don't mistake me for {namecode:44} or {namecode:45}...
302090.feeling4: Commander, should we go fishing today? Oh, there's work to do? I'll wait for you to finish then... Oh? No, it's fine! I'm more than happy to stay with you, Commander.
302090.propose: It's not for the other sisters in First torpedo squadron, but for me? Is that really alright? Ahh, this makes me happier than that one miraculous victory......thank you, Commander, I shall treat it as my most precious treasure.
302090.drop_descrip: Sixth ship of the {namecode:46}-class light cruisers, {namecode:47}.
302090.profile: {namecode:46}-class light cruiser, {namecode:47}. I've spent most of my time in the First Torpedo Squadron. Although I look aggressive, I actually prefer other things like fishing and just cruising around... just like when I was at Kiska. Perhaps protecting others is a more suitable job for me.
302090.touch2: Want to have a taste of my torpedoes, Commander?
302090.mission: We're starting a new mission. Got it?
302090.home: Did everyone make it back in one piece?
302090.win_mvp: I'm number one? Hm... I don't feel anything special...
302090.expedition: Commander, shall we return to port and do some fishing? The girls seem to be back from their commission as well.
302090.feeling3: I look trigger happy? I actually prefer being an escort more than I do engaging in combat...
302090.lose: Everyone, prepare to retreat... I'll cover the rear!

102290.detail: I can go underwater, but... I'm no submarine. I can't stay submerged for long...
102290.login: Huff... Puff... It's time for work.
102290.battle: Take a deep breath. The battle is starting...!
102290.feeling2: There's nothing in particular that needs doing right now. Commander... why don't you relax for a bit...?
102290.headtouch: You want to know more... about my mask...?
102290.mission_complete: Umm, Commander, I reminded you earlier, but... please collect the mission rewards at some point.
102290.main: July 9th... It's an important date for me.|Huff... Puff... Huff... Puff... Yes, let's try to relax...|Phoenix is a really hot-blooded girl, isn't she...? Compared to her... I might be pretty cold...
102290.feeling5: Even if you can't see my face directly, I want you to know that as long as I'm by your side, I'll always be smiling from the bottom of my heart.
102290.upgrade: Strengthening complete. Preliminary inspection in progress...
102290.unlock: Huff... Puff... I'm Boise of the Brooklyn class... Umm... Is there something I can help you with?
102290.feeling4: I'm not as straightforward as someone like Phoenix, but... Commander, I want to look after you more... E-even if I have to start with the finer details.
102290.feeling1: Commander, I don't get you at all...
102290.propose: Whether through my battles or my everyday duties, I always want to do something extra for you... If y-you're fine with that side of me, then... Huff... Puff... Y-yes! Commander, I'll be in your care!
102290.drop_descrip: Brooklyn-class light cruiser – Boise, Hull Number CL-47.
102290.skill: Pick out the biggest one... Mhm!
102290.profile: You'd like to learn more about what I did during that war? Well, I provided support for many landing invasions... The most memorable one? That'd be the one at Cape Esperance... Helena saved me back then.
102290.mission: Commander, there are still missions to finish. It'd be best to not forget about them...
102290.home: I'll look after the place while you're gone, so... don't worry.
102290.expedition: Here are the results from the commission... Please look over them.
couple_encourage: I'll leave the recon to you and your SG, Helena.
What are you talking about...?
102290.mail: Commander, there's new mail waiting for you. Please don't forget to read it...
102290.feeling3: When life knocks you down, get back up on your feet. These are words I try to live by... Commander, why don't you give it a try as well?
102290.lose: We've no choice but to retreat... I'm sorry, Commander!

101314.detail: Not only does she sell chocolate, she even wraps it up... Akashi's shop sure is convenient...
101314.touch: Commander, stop moving around... Let me get a little closer... Zzzzz...
101314.login: Just the two of us, all alone... Mm, we can talk about anything you'd like.
101314.main: Sleepy... Gonna put the desks together to make a bed...|Commander, since you accepted my chocolate, can I expect a reward...?|I also brought the chocolate that Helena prepared for you. Make sure to treasure it, okay?
101314.unlock: Commander, because you kept your promise and came... here's some chocolate, and a letter for you. Please read it later. No, it's not that big of a deal... Just a little embarrassing...
101314.drop_descrip: Commander, because you kept your promise and came... here's some chocolate, and a letter for you. Please read it later. No, it's not that big of a deal... Just a little embarrassing...
101314.home: Commander... stay with me a bit longer~

103081.detail: Commander, wanna put a karaoke machine in the office? Like, we should totally work hard and play hard!
103081.touch: Look, Commander! This place is a five-star recommended dating spot!
103081.login: Today's horoscope says... Romance... five stars?! Like, no way~!
103081.main: By the way, Commander, do you use any social media sites? They're quite popular among the girls, you know~ |Commander, what color nails do you prefer? Next time I get them done, I'll let show them to you~ |Club activities? Ahaha... I think I have a date with my sofa today...
103081.unlock: Huh? Commander? ... Wait, why are you staring at me like I'm some exotic animal? C-cute? Ehehe... Th-thanks...
103081.drop_descrip: Huh? Commander? ... Wait, why are you staring at me like I'm some exotic animal? C-cute? Ehehe... Th-thanks...
103081.touch2: Commander, would you prefer the pepper spray or a shot from my cannons?
103081.home: Oh, welcome back. Wanna go for some grub?

203072.detail: Jamaica, Z36... Through this arduous battle, I have met many companions who also see through the veil. Now, I am no longer alone in my Rebellion against Fate!
203072.login: You're back? Then let us continue. This time, the Unfathomable will respond to our summons!
203072.main: So, the first summoning failed. Such are the tribulations exacted by the Unfathomable. But I shall not capitulate so easily!|What's the matter, Commander...? Ah, could it be... the Unfathomable has left a clue upon my body?! |Bloody hell, if not for the fact that my Force is nullified by the slumbering depths' domain, I could delve even deeper in the search for Truth!
203072.unlock: O Unfathomable King of the slumbering depths, hear the call of my Force and step into this world through the Azur Gate! ...Huh, Commander? Why did you show up?
203072.drop_descrip: O Unfathomable King of the slumbering depths, hear the call of my Force and step into this world through the Azur Gate! ...Huh, Commander? Why did you show up?
203072.touch: Excellent, let us combine our Force and channel it into this magic circle.
203072.touch2: Ahh! ...No, can it be, your mind has been corrupted by the Unfathomable?
203072.home: Ohhhhh... The bastions of white sand were instantly reoriginated by the waves... such is the might of the Unfathomable Force!
203072.mail: The messenger has returned from the depths. Could it be a message from the Unfathomable?

203071.detail: The figure that suddenly showed up inside empty classrooms turned out to just be Eldridge. The mysterious stack of books in the library was nothing more than a Misdirection left by the Occult Club. And, the legends of the Ace who cloned herself to lead every sports club to victory; well, she was actually that incredible... But the Mastermind still hasn't appeared. Has my Investigation been misguided?
203071.touch: Until all Truths are revealed and the Mastermind's identity is brought to light, I cannot relent!
203071.login: Now then, let us begin today's Investigation! The Mastermind will fall into our trap sooner or later!
203071.main: Eyepatch? Nay. This is a tool that is necessary to seal off a portion of my Force. |Difficult Words, annoying Formulae... Curses, will I be defeated by these things before I am able to reveal the Truth?! |Exeter struggles with her Tests on a daily basis, but that is for the best. The true Tribulations are mine alone to bear.
203071.unlock: The school has recently been consumed by a series of Mysteries... there must be some Mastermind lurking behind the scenes. Yes, another Tribulation awaits me! I shall part the veil and reveal all Truths!
203071.drop_descrip: The school has recently been consumed by a series of Mysteries... there must be some Mastermind lurking behind the scenes. Yes, another Tribulation awaits me! I shall part the veil and reveal all Truths!
203071.touch2: Eeek! Just now, could it be... There's no doubt about it. The Mastermind took over your body to issue me a Warning!
203071.home: Without delving further into the Zone, we will not be able to uncover the Truth. Luckily, with you here, I will be able to enter realms normally inaccessible to me!

201060.detail: Commander, want to hang out together?
201060.feeling2: I'm full of energy today, Commander!
201060.mission_complete: Commander, I brought the mission rewards~
201060.main: Eh?! Y-You want to catch a rabbit? ...I don't get it, but for you, Commander, I'll give it a try!|Commander, what a nice weather today~ Let's take a walk, alright?|Hmm? Now that I think about it, I used to go to a lot of different places. ...Ah, Commander, I'll tell you all sorts of things about the places I have been to!
201060.feeling5: Commander, is there something I can do? Anything is alright, you know? You see, I'm happy being of use to you, Commander!
201060.upgrade: For your sake, Commander, I'm gonna work harder!
201060.unlock: I finally got a chance to meet you, Commander! I'm B class' Beagle! The best of what I can do are escort missions! If you need my help just let me know! I am quite a worker!
201060.feeling4: Commander, how about a walk? ...Walk by yourself? No no, it's not fun having a walk alone! I'm walking with you, Commander! Commander~ walk with me~!
201060.propose: Are you fine with giving me this...? Yes... I got it! Then for you, Commander, I'm gonna work extra, extra hard! Ehehe, I'm getting motivated!
201060.drop_descrip: B-class destroyer ー Beagle, Hull Number H30!
201060.profile: Self introduction? Huh... I didn't accomplish much, but I took part in many escort missions, you know? Norway, Atlantic, Operation Torch, and then... Anyway, a lot of those! It will be nice if I can be of help, Commander!
201060.expedition: Commander, the girls out for commissions have returned! How about we greet them? Come on, hurry up~
201060.mail: Commander, there's mail! Play with me after you're done reading it!
201060.feeling3: My hairstyle? Ehehe, it was born this way you know? It's as fluffy as a puppy~ Commander, wanna touch it?

901111.battle: Witness the power of the Le Fantasque class!
901111.main: Tired... Don't wanna work... Commander, don't call for me even if you have something that needs doing...|Ahem! Commander, I brought coffee! N-no way! How'd you figure out that I slipped cold medication into it...?!|I don't wanna do any more work todayyy... Commander, let's hurry up and take a break already~! Right! Now!
901111.unlock: Morning, Commander~ Mm, the Sabbath is the day of rest, so I shall not budge from my sacred charge even if you were to call Triomphant over. I solemnly swear to do absolutely nothing today.
901111.drop_descrip: Morning, Commander~ Mm, the Sabbath is the day of rest, so I shall not budge from my sacred charge even if you were to call Triomphant over. I solemnly swear to do absolutely nothing today.
901111.touch2: Hyah?! ...Jeez, what are you doing! Just when I was about to fall asleep...
901111.win_mvp: Extermination complete...... Wait, didn't I say I wasn't going to do anything today?!
901111.lose: I really can't get any work done today after all... I just want to head back and relax already...

203070.detail: Feel free to admire the manifestation of my Force, though this is just the tip of the iceberg
203070.touch: The flow of the Force, can you feel it?
203070.login: Back from your training? Come, Fate is calling for us.
203070.battle: Submit to the power of the Force!
203070.hp_warning: This is a trial of fate…!
203070.feeling2: I can feel the Force guiding our paths. Care to try out this new potion for me?
203070.mission_complete: Tribulations are not solely a quest for strength, but also the rewards along with it. Don't forget.
203070.main: This a special drink I've made, come, drink it and leave not even a drop!|The Force may be essential, but one mustn't drown in its power.|If battles are my destined Fortune then may they be even more fierce.
203070.feeling5: I cannot control the explosions in my heart…! Come, hold me tight and we shall join forces and defeat our foes… Eek!
203070.upgrade: I can feel it, the Force courses through my body!
203070.unlock: If you were able to find me then you are also a user of the Force, no? I'm York, the the magic-wielding York-class heavy cruiser. Let us fight against Fortune together.
203070.feeling4: This feeling.....Unmistakably, as long as you're by my side, I can unleash unlimited amounts of power. Is this the power born of our connected hearts, Love?
203070.feeling1: The attraction of my Force has diminished… Could that be because ultimately you were nothing more than a Faker…?
203070.propose: The time of the Promise descends upon us. O, Commander, take my hand and let us mend this world!
203070.drop_descrip: York-class heavy cruiser - York, Hull Number 90!
203070.profile: The nameship of the York-class heavy cruisers? That is merely an alias... One day I will conquer the Nightmare of Suda Bay, and become the Master of fate itself.
203070.touch2: Bodily contact holds no significance at all to such a noble soul… Aahh!
203070.home: It is necessary to rest after a battle. Come, have a drink and relax.
203070.expedition: The wheels of Fate spineths once more and we move yet closer to Elysium.
couple_encourage: Sisters! Join hands and fight!
You're a... Commander?
203070.mail: This... may be a communication from the Unknown.
203070.feeling3: … The attraction of our Friendship grows ever greater! Come, hold my hand, and let us commune!
203070.lose: Guh.... This is the Nightmare of Suda Bay!

305140.detail: I've noticed those Priority ships are strikingly individualis– Pardon, I mean they have striking personalities. Not that I'm jealous, or anything of the sort.
305140.touch: I will do as you order me to, Commander.
305140.login: Let's focus our attention on our work today. Don't be afraid to ask for my help, should you need it.
305140.battle: The Suruga Fleet w-will not disappoint...!
305140.hp_warning: Oh, for crying out loud! Just my luck!
305140.feeling2: I hope to leverage my meager secretary abilities for the betterment of the fleet. I'm always ready for your orders, Commander.
305140.headtouch: I hope my horns were left alone... Phew, they were... Err, no! Never mind I said anything!
305140.mission_complete: I've brought the mission rewards with me. Phew...
305140.main: I believe I'm better suited for a desk job where I can analyze data and draft new plans. The reason being my strengths lie in quickly reading, memorizing, and writing documents.|Reckless hotheads and I don't get along particularly well. So I've learned first-hand through bad experiences with a certain someone... That is not to say I hate those kinds of people, however.|I'm deeply grateful that you've elected me as your secretary. However, I would absolutely welcome the addition of more people to the office, as we're rather short-staffed with just me here.|I'm not a fan of battling, but if anyone picks a fight with me, then a fight they'll get. We were made to wage war, and so that is our responsibility.|Life is so peaceful at this port. For that, we can thank the many girls here who I don't hold as much as a candle to.
305140.feeling5: *Sigh*...! People have their eyes glued to me wherever I go now, thanks to you... There are plenty of other ways to express your love without embarrassing me, you know! Please, Commander, I'd rather not deal with that again!
305140.upgrade: It's meaningless to fight if you cannot win. As such, a few enhancements may prove necessary.
305140.unlock: Battleship Suruga, reporting for duty. It would seem that some threads of fate connect me to this port... No, don't mind my rambling. Please disregard that.
305140.feeling4: Look, I do appreciate your concern, but you saying that in front of everyone is embarrassing! Could you not put me on the spot like that again? That'd be great!
305140.feeling1: *Sigh*... I set myself up for disappointment by expecting any decent treatment... Can I at least ask you to not go too hard on me?
305140.propose: You have bizarre tastes in women, Commander... Anyway, this doesn't come as a shock to me; I've known for a long time that your feelings for me are sincere. I, Suruga, hereby accept your oath of love.
305140.skill: I'm gonna smash you to pieces!
305140.profile: I am Suruga, Kii-class battleship number three. I sadly wasn't constructed in time for that infamous war... It seems some threads of fate have led me to join this fleet, one I shall devote all my soul to. It is my pleasure to serve you.
305140.mission: I'd like to suggest completing these missions. It is your job to do as the commander, after all.
305140.home: Nicely done out there. Please don't mind me, go ahead and take some time to relax.
305140.win_mvp: Fools! I've– I mean, we've won!
305140.expedition: The commission team has returned. Shall we set out to greet them?
couple_encourage: Lady Nagato, I shall keep you safe from harm!
Kaga, please... don't go too far.
Amagi... I wish you could've been there for us...
If I wait just a little longer for my plan... No, I guess that's not happening...
Let's go, Kii!
305140.mail: It appears you have new mail. I'll confirm it on your behalf.
305140.feeling3: P-please! Offer your concern to other girls instead of me! You really don't need to constantly check how I'm doing just because I'm serving as your secretary!
305140.lose: Whatever, it's done and over now... Look, I don't want everyone to see this!

901110.detail: *Yawn*... Sleepy... I wanna go roll around in bed... Zzzzz... Geh?! Wh-what is it?!
901110.touch: Being elegant... isn't worth the effort... Geh?! Wh-what do you want?!
901110.login: Destroyer, Le Malin, is ready to take your orders at any time... *yaawnn*...
901110.battle: The blade that protects the Vichya Dominion advances!
901110.feeling2: Destroyer Le Malin is both your secretary and the blade that protects the Vichya Dominion. Please give me your orders.
901110.main: Without firepower, speed alone is not enough to defeat the enemy. That goes without saying. |So bored... maybe it's time to quit... Gah! I didn't say anything!|Dunkerque's handmade sweets... Guhehe... Ah, I mustn't! I'm still at work...!
901110.feeling5: Commander, t-today, can we leave work a bit earlier? ...It's not because I'm tired! Um, I was thinking... if you wanted to go on a date or something...
901110.upgrade: It wouldn't be right if I didn't work even harder.
901110.unlock: I am the mirage that chases the waves, the poisoned blade that protects the Vichya Dominion. Super Destroyer, Le Malin, is yours to command.
901110.feeling4: I, I can go home early today because I did such a good job...? Woah... Woohoo! Now I can head back and go to sleep! ...S-sorry, I got a bit excited there...
901110.feeling1: ...... (Le Malin seems to have fallen asleep)
901110.propose: As the blade that protects the Vichya Dominion, I, Le Malin, swear to defend you and offer you my eternal love. Um... this is really tiring... Commander, let's head back already...
901110.profile: I am Le Malin, Le Fantasque-class destroyer of the Vichya Dominion. I once fought alongside my friends of the 8th Light Division in Brest. After that, Le Triomphant went down a different path... Well, we don't hold it against each other.
901110.home: I steeped this tea just the way Triomphant taught me. ...So you knew, huh? Indeed, it's just a normal cup of tea. Please enjoy it.
901110.win_mvp: I've eliminated those who would stand in our way.
901110.expedition: The others have returned. Let's hurry and greet them.
couple_encourage: Welcome back... Le Triomphant.
901110.mail: This letter's for you, Commander... Is there nothing for me?
901110.feeling3: I, I did say that I was ready to take your orders at any time, but... there's just too much work after all...... Tired... Can't work anymore... Please let me go on leave...
901110.lose: I won't admit defeat... I haven't lost yet!!

304023.detail: Did my sand castle capture your interest? This was only possible because of the clement weather, after all~
304023.login: Commander, is this scenery to your liking? The blue skies and seas, and the merriment of friends frolicking on the beach...
304023.main: A seaside picnic might not be as lavish as the banquets I usually hold, but I am confident in my abilities to throw the best event possible~ Hehe, don't worry, some girls from the Eagle Union are helping me out. |The seagulls are flying into the distance. I wonder if they're splitting apart or reuniting... Hehe~|Oh my, staying under this scorching sun indeed seems bad for my skin... Commander, would you be so kind as to help me apply the sunscreen?
304023.unlock: We're headed for the white sands of the beach today. We all could use a breather every now and then, so let's just enjoy the sea breeze today. Hehe~
304023.drop_descrip: We're headed for the white sands of the beach today. We all could use a breather every now and then, so let's just enjoy the sea breeze today. Hehe~
304023.touch2: Commander, perhaps the sea breeze will help you come to your senses?
304023.home: Have you been enjoying your time here? Hehe~ If you get thirsty, please help yourself to this water.

304020.detail: Hehe~ Which do you prefer: matcha, or black tea?
304020.touch: I can take you anywhere the ocean reaches.
304020.login: There is nothing more relaxing than a banquet following a battle... By the way, Commander, I'm free after this...
304020.battle: Hehe, shall we go enjoy the festivities?
304020.hp_warning: Commander... It's too early to give up just yet!
304020.feeling2: Ehehe~ Commander, is there something on your mind?
304020.mission_complete: Hehe, shall we celebrate by holding a banquet tonight?
304020.main: *Sigh*... Whenever Kirishima comes to a banquet, all those kids that tag along with her usually end up making a mess of things... |When it comes to warfare, wisdom and courage are equally important. We can't count on another miracle if we discard proper planning and rely on blind courage. |Commander, I'll be able to protect you, no matter the situation. Hehe, I am called an "Imperial Ship" because I have that capacity after all~♪
304020.feeling5: Commander, after tonight's banquet... will you be free? Hehe, please look forward to it~
304020.upgrade: Today's breeze feels more pleasant than usual.
304020.unlock: I am the Imperial Ship Hiei, second of the Kongou-class, reporting for duty. Commander, where shall we go next?
304020.feeling4: Being able to see everyone's smiles at the banquet makes all the hard work and preparation worth it.
304020.propose: So this means... "We'll always be forever?" Thank you very much. I'll gladly accept it - however... If anything was to happen to us, I hope that you would consider yourself first...
304020.drop_descrip: Kongou-class fast battleship number two – Hiei.
304020.skill: Be swept away by the raging waves!
304020.profile: I am Hiei, the first Kongou-class battleship born in the Land of the Rising Sun. As an Imperial Ship, I witnessed the growth of our mighty fleet, and led our forces into the Battle of the Solomon Sea. Commander, have you finished your preparations? The banquet is about to begin.
304020.touch2: Hehe. Commander, have you not gotten enough sleep yet?
304020.mission: Let's finish while we still have the momentum!
304020.home: Welcome back. The tea has just been brewed to the right temperature.
304020.expedition: Welcome back, everyone. Hopefully, none of you encountered any suspicious people?
couple_encourage: Are you still waiting for your sister?
304020.mail: Are all of these new letters? Thank you for your hard work.
304020.feeling3: That Kirishima... She's actually quite the popular one...

408070.detail: Hehe, been oglin' me for some time, haven'tcha, Commander? I noticed ages ago!
408070.touch: You feelin' like some hide and seek? I'm game. I always win, y'see.
408070.login: Always happy to see ya, Commander. Today's lookin' like it'll be fun.
408070.battle: Oh boy, here we go! Listen up, folks! It's lunchtime!
408070.feeling2: You want a fun hunt, ya need good chums, else it's not happening~
408070.mission_complete: Commander, check out this mound of rewards we got~!
408070.main: This tail connector's not just for show. When plugged into my rigging: bam, gives me perfect control.|When I'm fighting, you can stare at me to your heart's content, y'know? Hehehe~|I just LOVE seeing my enemies squirming about, trying to get away from my attacks~ Ahahahah~!
408070.feeling5: I think we oughta get to know each other more intimately~ Whaddya say, Com-man-der? Ahahahah! Look at you, blushing! Oh, that's hilarious!
408070.unlock: Hmm... you're the commander 'round here, eh? I'm U-522, Iron Blood submarine, reporting for duty. Anyhoo, heard this here port's like a party. I'm eager to join in on it. Heheheh~
408070.feeling4: Commander, your cunning plans won't work on me. Cause 9 times outta 10, I know just what you're thinking.
408070.feeling1: Sure can't count on you, huh, Commander. Guess that's cute in a way, though?
408070.propose: I'm kinda worried about your future, what with how dang easy it is to read you, Commander~ But it's cool, I'll always be with you, so do keep counting on me, 'kay? Ahahahah~
408070.drop_descrip: Iron Blood Type IXC submarine – U-522.
408070.profile: I'm U-522, Type IXC sub, from the glorious 2nd U-boat Flotilla. You need long-distance commerce raiding, I'm your girl. Anti-sub escorts do put me in one helluva pickle, though. Anyways, keep those eyes peeled for my combat performance~
408070.touch2: Tail - no touch! Bad Commander! That's my sensitive spot!
408070.mission: Ya figure we got any new missions, possibly involving hunting?
408070.home: Mumph... Oh, you're back? Want some corned beef?
408070.win_mvp: That's all? Laaaame. I wanna have more fun~
408070.expedition: Commission team's back safe and sound~ Let's go check out those rewards.
408070.mail: Commander, got news for ya from headquarters~
408070.feeling3: Hey, you're pretty chill~ I'm feelin' like this is the start of a good relationship~
408070.lose: Oopsie... Guess I messed up a calculation...

408061.detail: It feels nice to kick back and enjoy some good music!
408061.touch: Commander, how about becoming the band conductor?
408061.login: Commander, let's put on some music!
408061.mission_complete: Commander, I'm all done with my homework. Let's go for a ride!
408061.main: Commander, I recently started learning the trombone, hehe. I'm not very good at it, but it's still pretty interesting. Wanna listen~? |If I was able to play this thing underwater, I'd be able to perform for the fishes! Too bad, though... Guess I'll have to settle for the fish in the aquarium!|Even though we U-boats hang out together regularly, studying together at school feels rather special!
408061.feeling5: I don't know why, but when it's just the two of us in the band room, my chest starts fluttering like I'm sick... but I'm so glad... Aghh!! I'm gonna go take Great Shark out for a spin!
408061.unlock: Commander, welcome to the school band! Why'd I join the band? The reason's simple – there's no Motorbike Club at school, haha! Just kidding~! Actually, I'm quite fond of music as well, heh.
408061.drop_descrip: Commander, welcome to the school band! Why'd I join the band? The reason's simple – there's no Motorbike Club at school, haha! Just kidding~! Actually, I'm quite fond of music as well, heh.
408061.touch2: Woah! I almost smashed this over your head...
408061.mission: Commander, there's a ton of homework today.
408061.home: Good work out there, Commander. Let's put on something chill~
408061.expedition: It's pretty far from here to the piers. Commander, how about we take Great Shark out for a spin?

901113.detail: This outfit is nice and smooth... Perfect for rolling around, right?
901113.login: Welcome back. Sure, let's keep it casual... I don't care either way, hehe...
901113.main: Le Triomphant is looking for me? Y-you're just trying to scare me! I d-don't believe that at all!|This outfit is great for rolling around on the comfy couch... It'd be a waste to not take a nap... Zzzzz...|It's time for a lunch break! ...What do you mean there's still more work to do? Let's just push it back to tomorrow...
901113.unlock: Zzz... zzz... Huh? Commander? I was in the middle of a nap... Oh, this outfit? It's cool, comfy, and cute. If you don't need anything from me, I'm going back to sleep...
901113.drop_descrip: Zzz... zzz... Huh? Commander? I was in the middle of a nap... Oh, this outfit? It's cool, comfy, and cute. If you don't need anything from me, I'm going back to sleep...
901113.touch2: Gwaaah?! Wh-where do you think you're touching! That scared me...
901113.home: Today's "scheduled break time" is still in effect for a few more hours. In other words... Please do it yourself.
901113.win_mvp: We won? ...Let's head back and go to sleep~
901113.expedition: The commission fleet's back? Y'know, I don't think I should be going outside, looking like this and all... So, you can go by yourself, Commander!
901113.lose: I wouldn't have signed up if I knew this was going to happen...

205031.detail: I wasn't really planning on dressing up at all. I was just a little curious, so... I-it looks good on me? ... T-thanks... Hey, don't get carried away!
205031.touch: If you try anything weird at all... then you'll be in a world of pain!
205031.login: I'll overlook your slacking at least for Halloween. But when this day is over, you don't get to slack off any more!
205031.main: Stop taking pictures, Rodney! I don't want people to see me like this...!|I guess it's okay to have fun with everyone like this sometimes... What? Did I say something funny?|What are you standing around for? It's a holiday; don't you have better things to do?
205031.unlock: This costume... *Sigh*, whatever. It's Halloween, so some kind of entertainment is to be expected. But listen here: I'm not dressing up because I WANT to participate, okay?!
205031.drop_descrip: This costume... *Sigh*, whatever. It's Halloween, so some kind of entertainment is to be expected. But listen here: I'm not dressing up because I WANT to participate, okay?!
205031.touch2: Do you wanna end up like this pumpkin?!
205031.home: W-what are you gawking at?! What's so weird about my costume?!

603021.detail: Did you do your stretches? You don't want your legs cramping up in the water.
603021.touch: Your eyes are wandering. Hehe, what's on your mind? You can tell me.
603021.login: Commander, please be careful swimming in the deep end, okay?
603021.main: Hey, no horseplay in the pool!|I really like swimming, but the submarines and destroyers are always faster... Why is that, Commander...?|Speed is one thing, but I'm quite confident in my stamina. How about it, Commander? Want to try me?
603021.unlock: Phew... It's a perfect day for swimming. Oh my, Commander, did you come to swim too? Or... perhaps you had something else in mind? Ehehe~♪
603021.drop_descrip: Phew... It's a perfect day for swimming. Oh my, Commander, did you come to swim too? Or... perhaps you had something else in mind? Ehehe~♪
603021.touch2: Really now, Commander? I understand your eagerness, but there's a time and place, no?
603021.home: Legs straight, calves stretched– Ah, welcome back, Commander. I suppose you can tell I've been teaching the others to swim. Would you like me to teach you as well?

304022.detail: I never expected this Spring Banquet to take on a life of its own... By the looks of things, everyone prefers it when the atmosphere is a bit livelier. Hehe~
304022.touch: Sake...? Hehe, since it's a special occasion, I wouldn't mind sharing a cup with you~
304022.login: Commander, you came at just the right time. The banquet is about to begin.
304022.main: Commander, make sure you remember to have your closing speech ready. All right? |You'd like... a red envelope as well? Normally, aren't you supposed to be giving out red envelopes to us? Heehee~ |During these times, it's best to just put aside your work and enjoy the festivities.
304022.unlock: I have to admit, these qipaos from the Dragon Empery are quite elegant... I might sound arrogant saying this, but I feel like this outfit really brings out my charm. Hehe, wouldn't you agree, Commander?
304022.drop_descrip: I have to admit, these qipaos from the Dragon Empery are quite elegant... I might sound arrogant saying this, but I feel like this outfit really brings out my charm. Hehe, wouldn't you agree, Commander?
304022.home: Putting your nose to the grindstone is commendable, but you should also know when to take it easy, Commander.

901112.detail: This hammock feels pretty nice, but I can't roll around... A tactical failure...
901112.touch: Swim? Hehehe, not to brag or anything, but I'll show you the most elegant way to float!
901112.main: Too bad you can't turn into an air conditioner, Commander... Otherwise, I'd cling to you all day... Zzzzzz...|In any case, Le Malin will now go take a most elegant nap. Don't bother me even if there's something that needs doing... and save me some Cola and snacks... Zzzzzz...|Who's that over there? ...Le Terrible?! C-c-c-commander! Hide me! If that girl finds me, I'm not gonna be able to sleep the day away!
901112.feeling5: Eh? It's already time to go home...? Geh! It's already evening! Hmm?! I can't move my legs because I overslept... Commander, help me...
901112.unlock: I must commend you for being able to find my secret base, Commander... but unfortunately for you, I refuse to return to the office today. Just... *yawn*...let me spend the whole day sleeping here...
901112.drop_descrip: I must commend you for being able to find my secret base, Commander... but unfortunately for you, I refuse to return to the office today. Just... *yawn*...let me spend the whole day sleeping here...
901112.touch2: I'm too slovenly...? Meh, haven't you already known that for ages~?
901112.mission: A new mission? Don't wanna... Th-there's ice cream in it for me? F-fine, I'll do it!
901112.home: The commander's out there working hard, but here I am... Zzz...
901112.win_mvp: Commander... Let's hurry back and turn on the air conditioning...
901112.lose: So hot...... Why must we sortie in this kind of weather?!

605010.detail: This may be unbecoming fo me to say, but nevertheless... It would delight me if you would use one of our baths. It would let you fully appreciate the splendor of our Empire.
605010.touch: Even I – the flagship of the Empire's fleet – enjoy leisure breaks from time to time. There will always come some downtime, no matter how tirelessly one works.
605010.login: May I offer you some succulent tea and a biscuit before you start your work for the day?
605010.battle: Eternal Flagship Vittorio Veneto, sallying forth!
605010.hp_warning: You hope to defeat me? With attacks this lackluster?
605010.feeling2: I never would've thought one day I'd sit down for teatime with Illustrious of all people. Fate is truly a strange thing, I suppose.
605010.mission_complete: Heehee. I think I know what you're thinking, Commander. "These missions are a cakewalk."
605010.main: The power of a cannon cannot be gauged by its caliber alone. Any who underestimate my 15-inch battery will pay dearly for their misjudgment.|I joined this fleet for two reasons – to achieve world peace, of course, and to further the Empire's influence. The latter of which I would like your assistance with, Commander.|Allow me to be curt, Commander. If you had the power to crush your opposition, would you still choose the path of passive deterrence? Would you choose a fleet in being?
605010.feeling5: I have gained many things in our time together – power, allies, and peace of mind. Please, Commander, I'm dying to know – what is it you desire from me in return? I can offer anything you seek...
605010.unlock: It's a pleasure to meet you, Commander. I am Vittorio Veneto, Eternal Flagship of the Sardegna Empire. Forgive me if I sound discourteous, but are you confident in your ability to command me?
605010.feeling4: I see not only my Sardegnian friends, but all members of the fleet, beaming with joy. How you managed this feat, I don't know, but it fascinates me to no end.
605010.feeling1: It seems I must reassess the Empire's future...
605010.propose: Do you comprehend the significance of this vow? Our futures are henceforth interconnected. I would normally not have accepted your proposal so easily, but your sheer passion won me over. Heehee.
605010.profile: Expectations of me were high already at my birth, when I inherited the flag following a horrific night. Ultimately, I failed to lead my loyal friends to victory... My past isn't all that bright, is it? But that is why I have high hopes in you, Commander.
