605010.touch2: Let it be known that this sort of behavior is abjectly inappropriate, no matter your motive for it.
605010.mission: Allow me to give you a reminder, Commander. You are in your right to delegate missions to me, your secretary.
605010.home: I have lunch planned later with ladies from the Royal Navy. Are you interested in joining us, Commander?
605010.win_mvp: Sardegna's hope, faith, and love shall be felt all across the world's seas, with our fleet as its emissaries.
605010.expedition: Were my tortellini to your tastes? I must make more to give to the returning commission team, you see.
couple_encourage: It is reassuring to have the backing of such capable allies.
Bow to the Empire's splendor!
May your battle go fortuitously.
605010.mail: May I offer a bit of advice? Choose your friends carefully.
605010.feeling3: Strenuous efforts on everyone's part will be necessary to spread the Empire's splendor across the world. That includes you, of course, Commander. Heehee~
605010.lose: The enemy overpowering you by sheer force is the most easily acceptable reason for a defeat...

203020.detail: You appear to have time, Commander~
203020.touch: If you don't do your work properly, even I will show an angry face for it. Com~man~der?
203020.login: Ah, have you come back, Commander? I was just about to go to your place~
203020.battle: I do not mind, but I really have to bring victory to Commander~
203020.feeling2: Do you need something? I'm concentrating on work right now, so spare me the sweet talk~
203020.mission_complete: The rewards have been distributed~ Or could it be~ that you want a reward from me?
203020.main: I am a little nervous when I am alone with you, Commander, but since you are alone I'm fu... fully calm myself~|Com~man~der~ Help me~ Please, you are the only one I can count on~|Did you know, Commander? Sometimes, making small mistakes can make one seem cuter~
203020.feeling5: Please mind the time, place and mood when you do this, so I'm sorry! ... Ah! I don't mind the amount of times you confess to me~
203020.upgrade: It's alright to not become stronger. I'm fine as long as I can be of use to Commander~
203020.unlock: London class' youngest, Shropshire, reporting for duty~ I've been told that I am air-headed and gullible, so I'll be giving you some problems~ Well then, my time awaits~
203020.feeling4: You are my type, Commander, but there are no specific reasons for me to like you so... I'm sorry!
203020.feeling1: Commander, you're in the way. Move aside, move aside
203020.propose: I'm sorry... is what you thought I was going to say? Well Commander, from now on, my life is your life~
203020.drop_descrip: London-class heavy cruiser – Shropshire, Hull Number 73!
203020.profile: The youngest of London class, and sent abroad away from my sisters. That is me~ Ah, it's not that I particularly wanted your sympathy, but if you give me a little bit of attention, I'll give you high points for that! ... Acting cute? Oh shush, I was being serious you know~
203020.mission: A new mission... If you finish it properly, I will re-evaluate you right away~
203020.home: You were dashing, Commander! I have to put in effort as well... Hmm, how about I heal your damaged heart from the battlefield, with my junior wiles?
203020.win_mvp: You need not shower me with praises. Pay attention to others as well~
203020.expedition: Commander? Staring at me is one thing, but you should also look out for the commission team. They have returned, you know?
203020.mail: Commander, you have new mail~ Is it a love letter? It's a love letter, isn't it? Open it, open it!
203020.feeling3: Commander, you are a good man and you have a prospective future. But after I think about it calmly, now is just not the time. I'm sorry!
203020.lose: Commander, clumsy girls have their charms as well, wouldn't you say? Heh-hey~

301790.detail: Oh, also, did you know my original name was "Destroyer No. 9"? ... I suppose it's a good thing they decided to change it.
301790.touch: Anti-air is crucial. Oh, also, the price one pays for negligence is much higher than you think.
301790.login: A commander should at the very least be on time. But considering your achievements up till now, you at least deserve some praise.
301790.battle: Don't think too hard, just do your part and we'll win. Let's go!
301790.hp_warning: Agh... So this is why they say you can't flee from pain...
301790.feeling2: If you'd like, perhaps I could give you a wise lady's advice on how to interact with others?
301790.mission_complete: Well... I wasn't expecting this big of a reward.
301790.main: I think Matsukaze feels compelled to worry about us so much, and sometimes we don't even know how we should respond...|If you want to slack off all day, just resign. Oh, also, you have much work left to do.|Kamikaze, could you stop teasing the Commander?
301790.feeling5: If something's on your mind, tell me. I may be old, but my experience has been useful for solving many problems. Besides, why would you hide anything from your partner? Ahah.
301790.upgrade: You needn't go so far for the likes of me... But I'm still grateful.
301790.unlock: You must be the Commander. I see... No, I'm not looking disgruntled. I'm Hatakaze of Destroyer Division 5. Oh, also, be ready. I will watch over you as your superior from now on.
301790.feeling4: Ah, you should also take this amulet. It will make you more sociable. But beware: if you use it to hurt someone, you will be too.
301790.feeling1: Could you acknowledge the error of your ways before other girls start thinking poorly of you?
301790.propose: It's me you want? But I'm not attractive, I'm just a bother who likes nagging about you... You're really not joking? I-if so... *Ahem*, then till the oceans of the world dry up, I will remain by your side.
301790.skill: It seems to be my turn.
301790.profile: I'm Hatakaze, a Kamikaze-class destroyer. Oh, also, though my class might make me seem experienced, not only did I mainly engage in escort missions and achieve nothing spectacular, my story ends with my wish to fight the bitter end, like Kamikaze did, going unfulfilled. For someone like me, that's rather deplorable.
301790.touch2: ... Now if you'd just use that bravery for something else, my view of you might actually change.
301790.mission: Those with talent work a lot. Do not leave missions incomplete.
301790.home: Admirable work out there. Have some tea and reflect on your tactics.
301790.win_mvp: A victory is merely a victory. Garishness and applause are needless.
301790.expedition: Before you go collect those mission rewards, remember to give thanks to those who worked so hard for them.
couple_encourage: Let's show them how veterans fight!
Shigure, don't get caught off guard.
301790.mail: Check the new mail you received. Oh, also, I have a copy of it as well.
301790.feeling3: Different people must be treated in their own unique way. This is no secret to social success, but it will help make you more sociable.
301790.lose: It seems I have not kept up with the times...

102089.touch: Can you feel my smartifying sparkly aura too, Commander~?
102089.login: Hey, Commander! Let Super-Smart Sandy handle all your work for today! It'll be done before you can say "no thanks"!
102089.main: Let's have a race, Commander! I'll be both your opponent and the referee!|Lalala la la~! Sing along with me, Sara!|You look bummed out, Commander~ How about we turn that frown right upside down?
102089.unlock: Heheh~☆ I have no idea what just happened, but I feel like I've gotten super strong! Commander, can you see my sparkly aura~?
102089.drop_descrip: Heheh~☆ I have no idea what just happened, but I feel like I've gotten super strong! Commander, can you see my sparkly aura~?
102089.home: Hokay, let's do this, Commander! ... Huh? You just got done?!

203019.detail: I can always change back to my old outfit, but to be frank, I've always looked forward to being able to wear something like this. Your Excellency, would you like me to get changed?
203019.touch: What am I going to do with you... Well then, Your Excellency, please rest for a while. I'll prepare the snacks.
203019.main: I feel like my mood has been changing since I got my new outfit. Your Excellency, would you like to go for some dessert in a little bit? |Your Excellency, please do not forget the fact that I am still your secretary ship. Now, please focus and get back to your work! |Your Excellency, did you know that Sussex said that this outfit looks really pretty? You don't hear words of praise from her often, hehe~
203019.unlock: Um... Your Excellency, could you please stop staring at me like you don't recognise me? I didn't think that I'd get a new look for my retrofit, either... But, don't you think it's rather cute?
203019.drop_descrip: Um... Your Excellency, could you please stop staring at me like you don't recognise me? I didn't think that I'd get a new look for my retrofit, either... But, don't you think it's rather cute?

203010.detail: What's the matter? Your Excellency, what are you looking at so seriously?
203010.touch: Bodily contact is... No, I don't mind. I'm just not used to it.
203010.login: Good day to you, your Excellency. I shall accompany you for today as well.
203010.battle: Everyone, please be mindful of yourselves. Do not get hurt if possible!
203010.hp_warning: There seems to be a slight miscalculation...
203010.feeling2: Your Excellency, a moment please. There's a bit of a problem here... Mmm, yes!... Is there anything you need?
203010.mission_complete: I've already made a list of the rewards. Please take a look at them when you have a moment.
203010.main: Your Excellency... have you seen Amethyst? I've been searching for her.|The Arctic was very cold. I still feel like i'm getting a cold from there...|My, this is a fine day. Erm, well... I thought it's a good time for a conversation...
203010.feeling5: Please stay still! I had already told you to dress yourself properly. And your hair... You can be far too casual with your appearance at times, your Excellency... Yes, that should do. Where do we go for our date?
203010.upgrade: I'm glad, but please mind the allocation of resources.
203010.unlock: First ship of the London class, London. Member of the First Cruising Fleet, while also having took part in battles of North Atlantic and Pacific missions. If there's a mission, rest assured and let me handle it!
203010.feeling4: A date? If your Excellency can finish all the work for the coming days, then there's no reason for me to refuse. How about it? Do you want to make the effort?
203010.feeling1: Your Excellency, please go elsewhere for your time. I shall handle everything here.
203010.propose: Thank you, please leave it there. More than that, look at this, Your Excellency... Surprised? Hehe. With our relationship, you should know why I'm not saying anything about this~ But, now that this is the occasion, let me handle the meal for today, with lots of what we like to eat.
203010.drop_descrip: London-class heavy cruiser – London, Hull Number 69!
203010.skill: Well then, I'm gonna try harder as well.
203010.profile: I am the lead ship of London class , London. I was a member of the First Cruising Fleet, and fought battles in North Atlantic and Pacific waters. Your Excellency, rest assured and leave the missions to me!
203010.touch2: Pl... please don't do such an improper thing!
203010.mission: Do your best to finish your missions today.
203010.home: Good work. I'll handle the official matters, so please go have some hot red tea.
203010.win_mvp: Being praised by your Excellency is the greatest honor to me.
203010.expedition: Yes, the commission is done on time. Let's verify the results, shall we?
couple_encourage: County-class sisters, now is our time!
203010.mail: Your new mail is right over here. Please confirm it.
203010.feeling3: Your Excellency, would you like to have tea together? If you're not done with your work yet, then please tend to it first. Of course, I will be with you.
203010.lose: ...I shouldn't be showing you manners when it comes to this.

202291.detail: Aurora also gave me this incense burner. It's supposed to be good for recovering from fatigue, so shall we give it a try together?
202291.touch: ...Hm? Already tired? You can lie down here if you'd like.
202291.login: Happy Lunar New Year. I'm glad I can see you today.
202291.main: Haah... Commander, I'm sorry... At this rate, this incense... is going to make me fall asleep... Zzzzz|The broth in the hotpot was as red as my clothes... It was a bit scary at first, but the food ended up being really delicious.|The pattern on this fan was embroidered. I learned how to do it from Yat Sen and the others a while back, but my hands were trembling so much I made a mess of things... Ugh, I wonder how everyone does this so well.
202291.unlock: Aurora chose this outfit for me because... the Spring Festival represents a time of celebration in the Dragon Empery, and red is the color that best symbolizes that. What do you think? Does this outfit... make you feel more festive?
202291.drop_descrip: Aurora chose this outfit for me because... the Spring Festival represents a time of celebration in the Dragon Empery, and red is the color that best symbolizes that. What do you think? Does this outfit... make you feel more festive?
202291.touch2: ...Um, Commander, I don't think... this is any way to conduct yourself.
202291.home: Commander, do you know about the Spring Festival? There are all kinds of interesting stories, and I'd like to hear more about that from you.

202280.detail: Between my idol lessons and shows, training and my maid duties, all to be useful to you, Master... It's a lot of work? You want to reduce my workload...? P- please don't throw me away...!
202280.touch: You need only ask and I'll be happy to shake your hand, or whatever you may want!
202280.login: Master, what would you have me do today? Idol things or maid things, I'll do anything you want!
202280.battle: Now, to steal Master's heart... with my dance!
202280.hp_warning: I can't let the Master throw me away...!
202280.feeling2: No longer a maid serving her master, I'm now an idol.I've learned so much from the other maids, but I'm still not sure if I can do this right...
202280.mission_complete: Master, here are the rewards. It's all thanks to their hard work.
202280.main: Singing is more about conveying one's feelings than it is skill... So I will keep singing for you, Master...|Madam Illustrious focuses so much on her footwork during dance practice... is it because of the mirror?|My fellow maids, and the girls from the different camps come together to make a proper idol unit. It's truly amazing that you can bring all of us together, Master.
202280.feeling5: I'm doing well as a maid, and as an idol...? I'm honoured by your praise! I'll keep working hard as an idol... No, I'll keep working hard in everything I do for you, Master!
202280.upgrade: I wonder if Albacore's idea could actually work...
202280.unlock: I am the light cruiser, Dido, currently taking part in idol activities as part of the experimental Muse System. I learned more or less what idols are supposed to do from the others, so p-please... keep a close eye on me!
202280.feeling4: You mean you're excited to see me as a maid, and as an idol...? Sorry, I misunderstood...
202280.feeling1: Did I let you down, Master? What a despicable maid I am...
202280.propose: It's unthinkable that a lowly maid could shine onstage with all of you... But I will redouble my efforts to be worthy of the honour! All for the sake of my dearest Master!
202280.drop_descrip: I am the light cruiser, Dido, currently taking part in idol activities as part of the experimental Muse System. I learned more or less what idols are supposed to do from the others, so p-please... keep a close eye on me!
202280.skill: As an idol, for the Master...!
202280.profile: I'm Dido, Royal Navy Light Cruiser. I'm but a lowly maid, and I never expected to be chosen to be an idol... But I'll do what I can!
202280.mission: We have a gig offer, Master. Won't you take a look?
202280.home: Master, are you hurt? Do you feel okay? I may be an idol for now, but if you need me, I can still service you anytime...
202280.win_mvp: I know I can do it if I work hard. I'll become an idol you can be proud of!
202280.expedition: Tashkent tells me the commission team is back.
couple_encourage: It's okay to show off from time to time...!
If only I could present myself to the Master like that!
202280.mail: Looks like some important mail, Master.
202280.feeling3: I look good in my idol outfit? Thank you so much, Master...! Oh, does that mean I'm not a maid anymore?! Master, you aren't going to abandon me, are you...?!
202280.lose: I can't sing as well as the Head Maid...

102221.detail: That's right! My sisters can take care of themselves for once! My only focus today will be enjoying myself at the party! ...Oh, who am I kidding, they can't go without supervision...
102221.touch: I'm beat. Saying hi to everyone isn't as easy as I expected... Oh right, makeup... Do I look okay, Commander?
102221.login: Hmm... Hope my lipstick looks fine... Commander? You're here already? O-okay, I'm coming!

202273.drop_descrip: Would you care for some afternoon tea, Commander? Heehee~ This is one of my little hobbies when I'm not performing my maid duties.
202273.home: Before you continue with your work, please enjoy a delicious slice of cake and unwind a little~

202243.win_mvp: Shall I uncork a bottle to celebrate the victory?

202240.detail: I am the Longbow of Crécy, and the Shield of the Realm... By your will, I am at your disposal.

202240.hp_warning: Do I carry on? Or do I retreat?
202240.feeling2: Commander, do you have something for me? I'm sure I can handle it.

202240.upgrade: Commander, have I really grown stronger?

202240.feeling4: You like sweet girls, do you, Commander? Well... hrrmm... What if I were to hug you like this? Would that make me seem sweeter?
202240.propose: The way you treasure me gives me such warmth and solace... This is what true happiness is, isn't it? Commander, please, I beg you, let us share in even more happiness...

couple_encourage: Once more, altogether then.

202240.feeling3: Commander, why are you laughing? Did something funny happen? Won't you please tell me too?

605011.detail: A shipgirl gazing out at the sea from atop a ship... It sounds almost like the setup for a joke! I'll have to tell Littorio about it later. Hehehe~

605011.login: Basking in the sunlight, feeling the sea breeze, and listening to the sound of the waves... Ahh, it's wonderful to have a relaxing day off.
605011.main: Only when you take the time to recline can you truly take in the beauty of the vast, blue sea. One day, we will have finally reclaimed it in its entirety. Won't we, Commander?|Are you going fishing, Commander? I see, then if you don't mind, I will take my leave for a while. I'd like to finish building my sand Colosseum.|Please do come and spectate our beach volleyball game later in the evening, Commander. If luck is on our side, you may get to see us go up against the Royal Navy's team.
605011.unlock: Nngh, haah... It's awfully sunny today... How long was I asleep, Commander? Oh, it's already lunchtime? In that case, I'll get started on some food. Would you like something as well?
605011.drop_descrip: Nngh, haah... It's awfully sunny today... How long was I asleep, Commander? Oh, it's already lunchtime? In that case, I'll get started on some food. Would you like something as well?
605011.touch2: Commander? I'm still awake, for your information.
605011.home: Would you care to sunbathe with me? It's delightfully pleasant, I assure you.

202232.detail: Hmm, what should we do next? Why don't we see if there's anyone who needs help...? Just sitting here idly somehow doesn't feel quite right...
202232.touch: If you're cold, p-please... feel free to use my shawl.

202232.main: Um, are you redecorating the office? Do you need me to help?|I got some red envelopes as gifts from my seniors in the fleet. Ahaha... I'm not sure how I feel about this...|Commander, the more free time everyone else has, the less free time you seem to― Um, oh my...

202232.drop_descrip: I agreed to try on this outfit, but... I know these fancy outfits don't suit me... H-huh, I look gorgeous?! ...Thank you very much. Even if you're just trying to make me feel better, I appreciate it...
202232.touch2: C-Commander... What if someone sees us...?!

102291.touch2: I, I don't think you should be doing this... *blush*

302040.touch2: Sometimes I really don't understand what you're trying to do, Commander...
302040.mission: If it's just taking a break once in a while, I think I can let that go.
302040.home: It's great to see that you returned safe and sound, Commander~!
302040.win_mvp: I hope every battle goes as well as this one did~!
302040.expedition: Commissions? That's part of my job too.
couple_encourage: {namecode:47} shouldn't always pester {namecode:45}...
302040.mail: Hehe, Commander~! You've got new mail~!
302040.feeling3: Commander? Oh, nothing. I just wanted to say hi!

202201.detail: No matter what clothing I wear, I am still your maid and live only to fulfill your expectations, my honourable Master.
202201.touch: Oh, my Master who has intoxicated me with passions so, it is an honour to have been chosen as your dance partner.
202201.main: Every single maid dreams of being able to stand beside her master in such a dress... Please forgive me for my presumptuousness... |This dress seems ill-suited for combat... but since it is your wish, Master, I shall humbly carry out your will. |This necklaces suits me well...? Thank you for praising this unworthy maid, my honourable Master.
202201.feeling5: Whether it's under the swirling lights of the ballroom stage, or in the smoke and explosions of the battlefield, there will never be anything more radiant than you in my eyes. My honourable Master, please allow me to gaze upon you and be at your side, always...
202201.unlock: My dear, I changed into the new outfit as per your request. I would be most grateful were you to offer me words of praise, Master.
202201.drop_descrip: My dear, I changed into the new outfit as per your request. I would be most grateful were you to offer me words of praise, Master.
202201.home: There is no greater happiness than your safe return, Master. Would you like to gather everyone to have tea?

202200.detail: My honourable Master, what would you like to learn more about today? Literature and culture? Logistics and strategy? The fine arts? Or, perhaps, you are more interested in more... carnal knowledge...?
202200.touch: Please refrain from intimate contact while others can see us, my honourable Master.
202200.login: It is good to see you return, my honourable Master.
202200.battle: Let us bring victory and glory to our honourable Master!
202200.hp_warning: As the Masters maid, I shall not be defeated!
202200.feeling2: I take honour in my service to you, Master. However, should you find my service unsatisfactory in any way compared to the Head Maid, I kindly ask of you to tell me.
202200.mission_complete: My honourable Master, the mission rewards have arrived.
202200.main: "Cleaning"...? If it is combat you are referring to, then I vow to meet all expectations you set for me, my honourable Master.|Regardless of what may ever happen, I shall always accompany you, my honourable Master.|Achieving a balanced diet is essential for one's health. Therefore, although my cooking skill may be unsatisfactory to you, please do not forgo the meals I prepare, my honourable Master.
202200.feeling5: I ask of you to stand proud and illuminate all the world with your glorious image, my honourable Master...!
202200.upgrade: My honourable Master, I shall become even more gorgeous for you.
202200.unlock: It is an honour to meet you. I am Sirius of the Royal Maids, here to assume the position. Henceforth, Master, I shall serve you to protect your glory and your beliefs.
202200.feeling4: If you find my embrace to be relieving, then I would gladly do so again at your command, my honourable Master.
202200.feeling1: ...I implore you to be more honourable, my slightly disappointing Master.
202200.propose: Oh, the bliss of getting to make this wondrous vow... Please, close your eyes for this unseemly maid and permit her to feel your warmth... My honourable Master...
202200.skill: My honourable Master, please grant me strength!
202200.profile: I am Sirius, the 5th ship in the 2nd group of the Royal Navy's Dido-class of light cruisers. I participated in Operation Pedestal in the past, but now I serve as a Royal Maid and have the privilege of fighting for my honourable Master.
202200.touch2: If you wish for me to service you tonight, then... M-my apologies! I made a rather careless assumption...
202200.mission: A mission of this magnitude is inconsequential. Isn't that correct, my honourable Master?
202200.home: It is good to see you return. There is tea and a light meal prepared for you. And, if you'll pardon my initiative, I have also prepared a creep... a crêpe. Would you like to have it now?
202200.win_mvp: My honourable Master, I have cleared the path so that you may move forward.
202200.expedition: My honourable Master, I have information regarding the results of a commission, so please relocate to the sofa and get in a relaxing position.
202200.mail: My honourable Master, the mail is here.
202200.feeling3: To me, there is nothing more honourable than to have the privilege of serving you, my honourable Master.
202200.lose: How shameful... My honourable Master, it seems I have made a mess of myself. Please give this naughty maid her due punishment.

202229.detail: You've noticed my new fittings? Don't worry, they will not impact the execution of my duties as a maid.
202229.touch: I've made some adjustments to my outfit as suggested by the others. What do you think, Master?
202229.main: "To improve is to change. To be perfect is to change often..." One should bear this quotation in mind.|Maintaining this new equipment takes significantly more time. I suppose that's the price of strength.|To study etiquette is to pursue knowledge. "Only in properly managing oneself is one fit to lead others..." Let's move forward together, Master.
202229.unlock: I am now more capable than ever of demonstrating the Royal Maids' style. Though I am not as talented as my sister, Curacoa, I sincerely hope you will find my service satisfactory. It is a great honour to work for you.
202229.drop_descrip: I am now more capable than ever of demonstrating the Royal Maids' style. Though I am not as talented as my sister Curacoa, I sincerely hope you will find my service satisfactory. It is a great honour to work for you.
202229.touch2: M- Master, what are you... Aie?!
202229.home: You must be exhausted. I have prepared today's tea with your comfort in mind. A maid must always be aware of her master's condition, as well as mood. Relax, and enjoy. Hehehe.

202220.detail: No matter the time or place, as a maid or as a soldier, one must always remember to observe proper etiquette.
202220.touch: Please be mindful of your posture. Be confident and stand tall so that you can earn the respect of others.
202220.login: Welcome back, Commander. Your tie is crooked... let me fix it for you. Your otherwise refined attire cannot be taken seriously with such a flaw.
202220.battle: Let's show our enemies what a Royal maid is capable of.
202220.feeling2: The details make up the difference between success and failure, whether in etiquette or in battle. Commander, please remember to always be attentive to details.
202220.mission_complete: A mission has been completed, but don't over-celebrate in an undignified manner, Commander.
202220.main: Royal etiquette is steeped in social and life philosophy. Please keep that in mind at all times. |I already am a perfect maid? Surely you jest... have you not met my elder sister yet? |Lately, your etiquette has improved greatly. However, don't get too proud, Commander.
202220.feeling5: Being with you reminds me of the time I used to live with my sister. She'd always instruct me on how to be a prim and proper maid. I wonder if I've managed to become... an excellent maid just like her...
202220.upgrade: I am one step closer to becoming a perfect Royal maid. Thank you, Commander.
202220.unlock: Greetings, I am your Royal maid, Curlew. The responsibility of supervising the master’s daily routine falls on the maid. I will help you become a Royal gentleman through and through, so please pay attention and work hard.
202220.feeling4: Just like libations, there is a time and place for drinking black tea. What, you want to have tea right now...? F-fine.. since it's been so long since you've had a break, I suppose there's no harm to it...
202220.feeling1: To think that there would be people who cannot comprehend Royal etiquette at all...
202220.propose: Since I have already made my oath with you, it would be improper if I was the only one instructing you. What would I like you to teach me? ...Master, can you please... teach me the etiquette of "love"?
202220.profile: I am Curlew, one of the Royal Navy's Ceres-class light cruisers. C-class light cruiser? N-no, that's not the correct classification, please don't use that term anymore...
202220.touch2: C-Commander... what is the meaning of this...
202220.mission: A new mission has been posted. Please complete it as soon as possible - it's rude to keep others waiting.
202220.home: Good work, Commander. I've prepared tea today according to your instructions from earlier. Please enjoy.
202220.win_mvp: As long as you strive for excellence, victory will naturally follow.
202220.expedition: Commander, a commission has returned. Please follow me to greet everyone who is returning. It's proper etiquette, after all.
202220.mail: This mail is for you. Don't worry, I'll be sure to leave when you are ready to check it.
202220.feeling3: Please do not blame me for being too strict. Royal etiquette is not something can be easily mastered.
202220.lose: It appears that I need to have higher expectations of myself.

305080.detail: I hate the phrase, "it's how it's always been done." The same mistakes will forever be repeated as long as fools keep spouting it.
305080.touch: Seeing as you have time to kill, why not practice your swordplay with me?
305080.login: Give me an engaging task, should you find one, Commander.
305080.battle: Hah, my rampage is soon to begin!
305080.hp_warning: Hahaha... Battles fraught with suspense are always the most interesting!
305080.feeling2: You are brave, lowering your guard around someone that could take your life at any moment. You say it's because you trust me? Hahahah. Trust. A fine word that is.
305080.mission_complete: A mission has been completed, has it? Then don't loiter around, go and claim the rewards at once.
305080.main: Brute force – the most primitive, but also most effective approach. That said, I much prefer fighting with words over swords.|I do not shy away from using any trick required to achieve my goals. I would rather that than play by the rules and end up at the bottom of the sea.|Stay behind if you cannot fight. The weak should know their place from the strong – this is the belief my sister holds.|I am neither as forward-thinking as Amagi, nor as short-fused as my sister. What? What's incorrect? The part about my sister, or my description of myself?
305080.feeling5: Your ambitions and dreams are of no concern to me, but I know that you need me. Which, I admit, is also true in reverse. Our fates are intertwined, and we cannot afford to lose one another... Hahahah, isn't that right?
305080.upgrade: You have an eye for talent, Commander.
305080.unlock: I am the nameship of the Tosa-class battleships, Tosa. I only serve those who I deem worthy. As for you... Well, I do not believe in making hasty judgments. For the time being, let me first assess your abilities.
305080.feeling4: When I am alone, I let no rules or regulations restrain me; I push my will through. However, when you are present, I feel compelled to follow the rules and act with prudence. You are really something else, Commander.
305080.feeling1: Weaklings belong behind the shorelines. I have no business with someone who cannot handle even a tidal wave.
305080.propose: Simply being given life in this world would've been enough for me, but now I've even been given a partner to spend said life with... Hmph, life is a long and arduous road, and I am happy that I get to walk it with you.
305080.skill: Bear witness to who reigns supreme!
305080.profile: I am Tosa, the first Tosa-class battleship. My construction began long ago, but its completion never came... I have been an aircraft carrier, a battleship, a weapons testbed, and a target; they worked and reworked me to the bone. But now I am here, in this form, and I will not disappoint you.
305080.touch2: Acting on a momentary impulse can have deadly repercussions. I do hope you're not getting any outlandish ideas.
305080.mission: A leader chooses their mission, not the other way around. You should take this principle to heart, Commander.
305080.home: Did you see anything extraordinary on your expedition? You may find it inconsequential, but I am curious to know what you encountered.
305080.win_mvp: It's over already? Hmph, I expected more from them.
305080.expedition: You don't expect me to announce when a commission team returns, do you?
couple_encourage: Together with me now, my sister!
I am still no match for you, Amagi.
305080.mail: A letter, eh? I would be grateful if even a third of the information in it is credible.
305080.feeling3: You are an odd one, remaining unfazed in the presence of the Sakura Empire's ships. Still, I do enjoy exchanging stories with you. What have you in store for me today?
305080.lose: Gah, so even I overestimate my abilities at times...

408020.detail: Are you sending me out? I can handle it by myself.
408020.battle: This is where you'll all sleep!
408020.feeling2: Your office is very quiet. I like it here.
408020.mission_complete: Rewards are in... You don't want to see them?
408020.main: Enemies nearby? Welp...|If you need someone to patrol, I'm good to go anytime.|Such a quiet office... I approve.
408020.feeling5: I've spent thousands of hours swimming through the dark depths of the ocean... But lately all I can think about when I'm out on a mission is the warmth and light of your office... I think... I think I need to be with you, Commander.
408020.unlock: Type VIIB submarine, U-47. I don't like crowds... If that's all, I'll be in my room.
408020.feeling4: I can visit anytime I want? Thanks... But... For some reason, I feel like I can't really relax here... I'm always on edge...
408020.propose: I'm meant for more than just voyaging through the cold, dark oceans. My place is here, at the port, by your side... When I'm with you, even just sitting in silence, I feel... happy.
408020.drop_descrip: Iron Blood Type VIIB submarine – U-47.
408020.profile: I'm U-47. I went behind enemy lines at Scapa Flow and sunk Royal Oak. I'm going to go out, sink the enemy, and come back. Just like I did then.
408020.touch2: You looking to take a nap at the bottom of Scapa Flow?

408020.expedition: Looks like the commission team is back... There's a lot of them. I don't want to go...
couple_encourage: Wolfpack... the hunt is on!
408020.mail: New report is in... I hope the enemy doesn't crack our codes...
408020.feeling3: So like, I can't really help with your work at all... But you'll let me stay here... You don't mind?
408020.lose: So this is how it ends...

105130.detail: Hmm, you want to know how well I fight?
105130.touch: Don’t touch me as if you’re trying to be intimate with me.
105130.login: Welcome back... how does my smile look? (Forcibly smiles)
105130.hp_warning: I won't let go of victories to my enemies!
105130.feeling2: What must I do to possess a good smile... think about the things I like? If so, I feel very happy even at the thought of winning against South Dakota... muahahaha...
105130.mission_complete: Go grab the reward yourself, I’m not interested.
105130.main: My smile looks beautiful? You jerk... oops, keep smiling, keep smiling. Thank you for your compliments. | Hey, that rigid South Dakota is still the same. Commander, you see, I am cuter than her. | A true measurement of friendship is their actions and not their words, I don’t like people who are rhetorical in nature.
105130.feeling5: I couldn’t help but smile when I saw you, this is the first time that I’m feeling this way... although, I also have other feelings rushing towards me. I suddenly want to see your expression when you are bullied by me—— Commander, stay with me for a while. (Laughs)
105130.upgrade: It feels so good to become stronger.
105130.unlock: Hello, Commander, I am Washington... my sister told me that I cannot be so rough once I join the fleet, so I am practicing my smile. Darn, why must I listen to her...
105130.feeling4: Lately, my smile has become more natural? Emm, huh (scratches head), I was recently trying to find a new hobby. While I was searching, I realized that being with you is not so bad… (whispers)
105130.feeling1: You are too weak, it’s no fun playing with you, go practice some more.
105130.propose: Wait wait! We’re doing “that”, right? Is this your new way of teasing me!... Damn, you bastard, I’m not sure if I should cry or laugh about this...
105130.drop_descrip: North Carolina class battleship— Washington, hull number BB-56.
105130.skill: Out of my way. I'm ready to fight!
105130.profile: North Carolina class ship no. 2. I am Washington! The thing I like to do the most is to destroy my enemies. Recently, I am practicing on my smile. —— Battle record? I don’t really show off with such things, all in all, how’s my smile?
105130.mission: A new mission? Haha, now my blood is boiling.
105130.home: I’m glad that you didn’t get hurt—— What?! I don’t have feelings for you!
105130.win_mvp: Sure enough, I am happiest when all the foes are annihilated~
105130.expedition: Your memory can’t be worse than mine, right? The commission fleet has returned, won’t you go greet them?
105130.feeling3: No, no, that’s not right. If we do it this way, won’t it end much the same like in the past? … Don’t try so hard? You sometimes say stuff like that… Hmm? That was a good smile from me just now?
105130.lose: Oh, I will not forget you!

302041.detail: Commander, how do you plan on spending your Spring Festival? Me? ...Well, chilling in my room with a cup of tea sounds pretty good, or reading a book, or rolling around. Ehehe~
302041.touch: Commander, want me to clean your ears too? Sure, come here then~ *pat* *pat*
302041.main: Commander, have you seen Kinu? I told her I'd clean her ears, but she sure bailed quick... Seriously, what's wrong with cleaning your sister's ears...?|Commander, you know, Abukuma started having tea with me, and will even let me clean her ears! Ehehe, th
302041.feeling5: Whispering to you while cleaning your ear like this... kind of makes it seem like we're a couple, doesn't it? Hehe, forget I said anything. All right, all done. You can stay here and chat a bit more if you'd like~?
302041.unlock: Good evening, Commander. This room...? Ah, it's a special Dragon Empery-themed set I bought from Akashi's. It looks pretty snazzy and was on sale, so I picked it up. Ehehe~
302041.drop_descrip: Good evening, Commander. This room...? Ah, it's a special Dragon Empery-themed set I bought from Akashi's. It looks pretty snazzy and was on sale, so I picked it up. Ehehe~
302041.touch2: Jeez, Commander, don't blame me if I poke a hole in your eardrum~
302041.home: Look, Commander, the tea stalk is floating upright. I'm sure something good is going to happen today~

10700050.detail: It's important you closely read an idol's bio to grasp all her strengths. Take all the time you need.
10700050.touch: You need a hand with your work? Of course! I'll make sure everything comes out looking flawless!
10700050.login: Let's have a look at our schedule and see what we have to do today, Commander.
10700050.hp_warning: I'm not giving up until it's over...!
10700050.feeling2: Ah, Commander! Just who I was looking for. Do you have a full-length mirror anywhere? I could really use one for dance rehearsal.
10700050.headtouch: Goodness gracious, your hair is even messier than mine, Commander. Please, for your own sake, pay a little more attention to your appearance!
10700050.mission_complete: Great! You've finished that task. Don't forget to claim the rewards.
10700050.main: Oops. Sorry for spacing out, Commander. I'm juggling several things at once right now...|It's good we all came here together, but that means things are as hectic as ever... Hey! Ami! Mami! Get back here! What are those shovels for?!|If we spruce up our choreography a bit, it should take our performance to the next level. Let's do it! We'll rehearse it for our next show!
10700050.feeling5: I've learned so much and gained experience I never would've otherwise by watching you work. I feel my horizons have expanded to the point I can come up with novel new strategies!
10700050.upgrade: Steady progress! Everything is going exactly according to plan!
10700050.unlock: Pleased to meet you. My name is Ritsuko Akizuki. I was wondering what was going to happen to me when I suddenly got blown away, but... In any case, I'm pleased to make your acquaintance!
10700050.feeling4: Your job description has a lot in common with that of a producer's. I feel I could learn new things by watching you, actually... Would you mind letting me do that, when you have time?
10700050.feeling1: What about our last concert could we improve on...? Oh, excuse me, but I don't have the time right now.
10700050.propose: The things I've learned here will prove invaluable for my career, moving forward. So, allow me to say it once again: Thank you for everything, Commander!
10700050.drop_descrip: Pleased to meet you. My name is Ritsuko Akizuki. I was wondering what was going to happen to me when I suddenly got blown away, but... In any case, I'm pleased to make your acquaintance!
10700050.profile: My name's Ritsuko Akizuki. I always give everything my best shot! And that includes working as an idol at this port. On a related note... Wow, you have a lot of shipgirls with potential starpower!
10700050.touch2: Commander! Your time is better spent on doing work than doing... that!
10700050.mission: There's still work left for us to do! Chop-chop! Let's wrap it up quick!
10700050.home: Good to see you back, Commander. Take a moment to relax before our next task.
10700050.win_mvp: We've completed the job. Just as I predicted!
10700050.expedition: Those girls are back from their commission. Hellooo? It's time to get up and welcome them back, Commander!
couple_encourage: Mami! No more mischief, got it?
Where have you been, Azusa?!
Haruka, your could improve you choreography by doing it more like... This!
10700050.mail: There's new mail for you. Best to read it now, before you forget.
10700050.feeling3: Well done today, Commander. You're keeping yourself busy as always. Say, do you need help with something? I've got some spare time right now.
10700050.lose: I suppose this means my prediction was wrong... I'll have to fix the kinks in the system!

307061.detail: I'm giving off a different vibe from usual? Hehe, I'll take that as a compliment! As a matter of fact, I do like trying on different outfits from time to time for a change of pace.
307061.touch: Huh? What's the matter, Commander? Is there some place you'd like to check out?
307061.login: Commander, how should we begin our work today? Allow me to aid you!
307061.main: Akagi isn't exactly a fan of these large gatherings... Wait, could she be antisocial?! Err, that doesn't seem right... |T-Taihou?! You can't do that kind of stuff in public! Commander too, you should keep your distance! Stay hidden until I say otherwise! |Commander, would you like something to eat? Can't grow big and strong without good food, you know~ Hahaha, just kidding!
307061.feeling5: As long as there is someone I want to protect, I won't fear the strongest of enemies or the the sting of defeat. No matter how many times I am knocked down, I will always persevere and claw my way back up. No matter what happens, Commander, I will always protect you and Shoukaku.
307061.unlock: New Elite 1st CarDiv, Zuikaku, reporting for duty! Ahh, I've always wanted to give such a cool introduction! Shoukaku would definitely make fun of me if she heard it, but I wanted to try it while everyone is in a festive mood... Commander, what'd you think?
307061.drop_descrip: New Elite 1st CarDiv, Zuikaku, reporting for duty! Ahh, I've always wanted to give such a cool introduction! Shoukaku would definitely make fun of me if she heard it, but I wanted to try it while everyone is in a festive mood... Commander, what'd you think?
307061.touch2: Uhh... So you wanted to compare mine to Shoukaku's after all?
307061.mission: This is nothing compared to Mikasa's hellish training! I'll be done in no time!
307061.home: Phew... I'm in a pretty good mood, but that was still pretty tiring... Commander, can you bring me something to eat?
307061.win_mvp: Victory is assured as long as I'm here!

202210.detail: It is said that a woman's charm is greatest when in front of a lens... Commander, I trust that you'll bring out my best side~
202210.touch: If there is anything you need, please call for me right away~
202210.login: All the preparations are complete, Commander. Please give your orders - I will delegate tasks to ensure that our missions get finished.
202210.battle: We'll carry forth our tradition of "meeting our enemies head-on." Let's charge forward heroically!
202210.hp_warning: It's do or die... I have to go all out!
202210.feeling2: Would you like some snacks? My old students used to love these - please have some.
202210.mission_complete: Commander, we should arrange to collect the mission rewards.
202210.main: A fly? Don't worry, they'll disappear after a few moments~ |To have a junior as exceptional as Belfast... I have to redouble my efforts~ |I have already cleaned the office, Commander. I would imagine that having a comfortable work environment is of great importance to you.
202210.feeling5: Whether as a maid, or as your partner, I am happiest when you rely on me, Commander.... Hehe, this is today's snack. Please have some~
202210.upgrade: My anti-air capabilities have been upgraded. Great~!
202210.unlock: Though this is the first I'm meeting you, I can't help but to feel a sense of familiarity from the bottom of my heart... I am Curacoa - from now on, allow me handle the various affairs around port. Please look forward to it!
202210.feeling4: Sometimes, I think about what I would do if I had a day off from maid duties... Oh my, it seems that I can wholeheartedly focus on serving you today, Commander.
202210.feeling1: My apologies, but I believe it would be best if we maintained some distance.
202210.propose: Right now, I am convinced that there is nothing happier than being in your arms, Commander. Please take care of me from now on, my beloved Master~
202210.skill: Please be at ease. I shall always be here~
202210.profile: I am Curacoa, light cruiser of the Royal Navy. I've served in several wars, so my combat experience is fairly rich. I hope that I'll be able to train some children to carry on our duty.
202210.touch2: Are you trying to flirt with me? Perhaps... there might be a better place for that.
202210.mission: It's not good to let missions pile up. Should I plan them out for you?
202210.home: Good work during the sortie. Want to take a breather so you can think about your next step? There's plenty of time to spare, so make sure to cherish your health.
202210.win_mvp: To think that I'd get MVP... sorry about that~
202210.expedition: Shall I greet the girls who are returning from commissions?
202210.mail: Mail has arrived. There appears to be no bad news anyway.
202210.feeling3: Commander, would you like to come to my next lecture? It would be a great encouragement to all the girls.

202199.touch: In the interests of fairness, I think I should be toying with you next time?
202199.battle: Let's get the senseless violence over with, and then have ourselves a picnic.
202199.main: My quiet, peaceful life has been riled like these waves, and you need to take responsibility for that.|...All your staring at me is quite a big hindrance to my work. If you have something you need from me, maybe you could wait until I'm finished?|Looking to the future has never been one of my skills... Do you think you could take care of this one for me?
202199.unlock: I've got an all new outfit here. Does it please you...? Hehe, seeing you all giddy like that is going to rub off on me as well.
202199.drop_descrip: I've got an all new outfit here. Does it please you...? Hehe, seeing you all giddy like that is going to rub off on me as well.
202199.touch2: ...Don't you think you'll regret it if you keep going?
202199.home: Welcome home. Would you like dinner, a bath, or would you like... A nice, soft hug?

102020.detail: Make sure you ask me any questions if you're lost before we head out!
102020.touch: Please don't tug me like that... I'm not a kid!
102020.login: Hello, Commander. I've been waiting for you. Oh my, look at the time! Shouldn't we start the training now?
102020.battle: Please pay attention, everyone! This is a good chance to get some real combat experience~
102020.feeling2: Commander, mature people like you need to pay attention on the job.
102020.mission_complete: Please don't forget to claim your mission rewards.
102020.main: Shall we begin our training, Commander?|For a beginner, every bit of training is very important~!|My name is Raleigh, not... that! Also, don't forget the "Ms."!
102020.feeling5: You're calling me 'professor' in such an... interesting way when we're alone. Are you expecting to receive private lessons? You're just like a little kid, Commander...
102020.upgrade: Now I can properly mentor you, Commander.
102020.unlock: I'm Raleigh, the Omaha-class light cruiser. Please sign this contract here... There we go. I'm hoping we'll make a good team from now on, Commander.
102020.feeling4: You've been taking it pretty easy recently, Commander... *Sigh*... I guess some of the blame is mine to share... It's hard to be strict with someone I like...
102020.propose: To receive something so precious from a student... I should be ashamed to call myself a professional mentor... But you make me...
102020.drop_descrip: Omaha-class light cruiser – Raleigh, Hull Number CL-7!
102020.skill: Let me show you some textbook maneuvers.
102020.profile: I'm the training officer of the Omaha-class fleet - Raleigh. I'm going to be very strict with anyone who won't listen to what I say!
102020.touch2: I'm not immune to getting angry, you know... Co-man-der!
102020.mission: Commander, please don't forget about your unfinished missions!
102020.win_mvp: You can't use the same trick on me twice!
102020.expedition: It's almost time, Commander. I'll go ahead and welcome the girls back from their commission.
102020.mail: Your mail has been sorted. Remember to read your messages thoroughly, please!
102020.feeling3: You want to know more about me? Hmm... you may be the first person to treat me like an equal. I'm happy about that, I suppose.
102020.lose: Phew... That was close... I nearly...

301123.detail: If you combine both of our wings, there might not be much room left on the screen... Why don't you edit it in and see for yourself, Commander?
301123.touch: Commander, shall I bring you something to eat or drink?
301123.login: Commander, I'm glad you haven't forgotten the promise you made with me and Ikazuchi.
301123.main: Akatsuki said she wanted to join us so we can have a 6th DesDiv get-together at the party, but she seems to have gotten lost on the way... I hope Hibiki is able to find her.|"The moon is beautiful tonight" is supposed to be a pretty famous line, right? Eh... How'd you already know about it, Ikazuchi?|Ikazuchi seems to have brought you some strawberries. Judging from your expression, I'm... supposed to bring you blueberries?
301123.unlock: I'm the fairy of lightning that illuminates the stars in the night sky... So that's what we're going with, huh. Commander, will you accompany me to the party?
301123.drop_descrip: I'm the fairy of lightning that illuminates the stars in the night sky... So that's what we're going with, huh. Commander, will you accompany me to the party?
301123.home: Whether you are fighting, taking care of commissions, or just checking daily missions, I will always be waiting for you here.

202190.detail: You'll have to get a bit closer if you want to share this umbrella.
202190.touch: It's like... a couple of small animals playing with each other. Hehe!
202190.login: Would you rather have a cup of coffee, a spot of tea, or a splash of pale ale before work?
202190.battle: Such a lovely day. Let's get this pointless fighting over with quickly.
202190.hp_warning: Phew... It's a good thing I bought that insurance.
202190.feeling2: Rest assured. I will perform my duties to your expectations.
202190.mission_complete: Hard work is not always well rewarded... But it seems this time at least, luck was on our side.
202190.main: While I may not have as many battle commendations as my younger sisters, I'm confident none of them know how to enjoy life quite like I do.|I'm no good at these cat and mouse games. Sigh... Why don't you just have a seat and we'll talk like normal people...?|Everyone comes into this world with all kinds of hopes and dreams... But not everyone will lead a life full of adventure and surprises.
202190.feeling5: If you take your eyes off me, you never know when I might take up my umbrella... and fly away with the wind♪
202190.unlock: I thought I had gotten lost, but how fortunate that I ran into you. I am the Town-class light cruiser, Newcastle. Thank you for looking after my sisters.
202190.feeling4: Your smile reminds me of the wind in my hometown... it's that warm, westerly breeze. Hehehe.
202190.feeling1: I have trouble keeping people at a distance. I apologize if this has caused any misunderstandings between us.
202190.propose: ...It's remarkable how you've turned this ordinary, quiet life into something so unforgettable... Aah... I feel like my heart is about to beat out of my chest with happiness and satisfaction. How will I ever be the same again...?
202190.skill: Glory to the ordinary, the commonplace!
202190.profile: I am Newcastle of the Southampton subclass of Town-class light cruisers. While my record is one of the longest, I also somehow had the most free time... It would be nice if I could make it to retirement safely this time as well.
202190.touch2: ...You like my soft bits so much, do you? Now then, what if I were to give you a nice, soft, satisfying embrace?
202190.mission: It's work that must be done, but we can do it at your pace.
202190.home: Welcome home. Let me take your coat... You're unharmed, thank goodness.
202190.win_mvp: This victory drink is a bit strong for me... I think I'd better hand it off to you.
202190.expedition: A familiar scent rolls in on the sea breeze... the girls are back. Shall we head out to greet them together?
couple_encourage: There's no need to rush on ahead... I can't keep up with you like that.
202190.mail: Mail for you... Do you think perhaps it's from me?
202190.feeling3: The weather report says rain today. Do bring an umbrella if you need to go out.
202190.lose: I've brought such trouble upon you once again... what a dreadful shame.

301111.drop_descrip: {namecode:13}, {namecode:13} has been transformed into tea! What should we do! {namecode:14} and {namecode:13} will get slurped up by the Commander!

101259.detail: How long are you going to keep looking... I want to go see how Yorktown is doing...
101259.login: You're a full-blown pervert beyond saving if just seeing these clothes makes you so excited!
101259.main: nil|As long as you promise to work hard, I'll stay with you for just a little longer... I guess?|nil
101259.unlock: I'm just wearing new clothes, so why should I have to raise my skirt like this? Huh? You want me to look more upset? You... you pervert!
101259.drop_descrip: I'm just wearing new clothes, so why should I have to raise my skirt like this? Huh? You want me to look more upset? You... you pervert!
101259.home: Good work out there... W-what! I'll give a decent compliment to someone who works hard, even if they're stupid!

307060.detail: That Grey Ghost... I’d like to duel her just once.
307060.touch: My least favorite food? Turkey, of course.
307060.login: Where are we going today? Pearl Harbor? Or perhaps the Coral Sea?
307060.battle: A never-ending swarm of enemies? I’m already used to it.
307060.feeling2: Seniors and juniors... they’re all such a pain.
307060.mission_complete: Hmm... Seems like the situation has taken a turn for the better!
307060.main: {namecode:95} is so cute when she’s embarrassed!|Keep fighting until the last arrow is broken! That is what it means to be an elite!|Wait, Grey Ghost, don’t run away just because you won! Let’s have a rematch!
307060.feeling5: Commander, you make me feel just as if I am with Shoukaku. H-huh? That’s not it! I’m not treating you as my sister!
307060.upgrade: As a perfected aircraft carrier, I shall not lose to anyone, not even to my seniors or to the Grey Ghost herself.
307060.unlock: I am {namecode:96}, the last elite of the Sakura Empire’s Carrier Divisions. I can only be at my best when I am with my sister {namecode:95}.
307060.feeling4: Whenever I feel irritated or lost, training always makes me feel at ease. Yes, I’ll definitely get stronger and catch up to that Grey Ghost one day.
307060.feeling1: Commander, would you like a taste of the anguish I experienced during the Battle of the Marianas?
307060.propose: E-eh?! Th-this is... I’m not misunderstanding you, right? Then... um, from now on, I’ll be in your care, dar... darling? Waaah! Shoukaku is calling me!
307060.drop_descrip: Second ship of the {namecode:95}-class aircraft carriers, {namecode:96}.
307060.skill: As long as Shoukaku is with me~!
307060.profile: I’m {namecode:96} from the Fifth Carrier Divison, though I was assigned to the First Carrier Division at one point. Together with my sister Shoukaku, we became the last two elite carriers of the Sakura Empire. We triumphed in bitter battles against Lexington, Hornet, and even Enterprise. That’s right, I was even able to severely damage the Grey Ghost herself, although she proved to be luckier than me. My service came to an end when Lexington, risen from the dead, sunk me. In the end, I still completed my final mission and sank with no regrets.
307060.mission: Is it time for a break? Commander, you should come try some of {namecode:95}’s cooking!
307060.home: I’ll need you to perform some maintenance on me. Ah, don’t forget about the planes either!
307060.win_mvp: I am the auspicious crane, after all!
307060.expedition: If only I had more planes...!
couple_encourage: I'm fearless, as long as my sister is with me!
I don't know why, but I just find you terribly annoying...
That ties up the score. Next round decides the winner!
Uwah! When did you get here?!
I never thought I'd fight alongside the Grey Ghost herself!
307060.mail: So? Is it good news or bad news?
307060.feeling3: My fate always seems to be entertwined with Lexington’s... Ah~ Commander, please don’t tell Sara I said that. I can’t handle that girl.
307060.lose: Am I going to be sunk... again...?

102090.login: Hey, Commander! You seem to be in a good mood today!
102090.battle: I'm in a hurry... just come at me all at once, alright?
102090.feeling2: What is, Commander? Something troubling you? I've got lots of little sisters, so I'm used to giving them my shoulder to lean on. So if anything's got you down, just tell me.
102090.mission_complete: Nice! We got some mission rewards!
102090.main: Never regret the choices you make!|Why do you call me "Clevebro"?! I'm a girl, just like the others!|You know, I like trees. Let's grow a bonsai, Commander!
102090.feeling5: I feel like I've told you everything about myself... Time sure flies, doesn't it... I doubt someone who understands me the way you do will ever show up again. That's why I've...
102090.unlock: Pleasure meeting you, Commander! I'm Cleveland, a knight of the sea! Come on, time is money! We can't afford to take a break!
102090.feeling4: Before I realized it, I'm the one who's leaning on your shoulder instead... but hey, that's fine. We can always just rely on each other.
102090.feeling1: Sorry, my sisters are waiting for me. I don't have time to deal with you.
102090.propose: Heh, I had a feeling this would happen! From now on, you can tell me anything. I'll take excellent care of you!
102090.drop_descrip: Cleveland-class Light Cruiser – Cleveland, Hull Number CL-55!
102090.profile: I'm the big sister of the Cleveland-class... but I guess that's obvious from my name alone. I fought through the Battle of Renelle Island, the Battle of Empress Augusta Bay, plus many others, and I earned around 13 battle stars, so I'm pretty strong!
102090.touch2: You can't do this sorta stuff in public, Commander...
102090.mission: We've got a new mission! Let's finish it in one go!
102090.home: Ah, Commander, let me give you a massage... Just bear with me!
102090.win_mvp: Hehe, now this is what I'd call the fruits of my hard labor!
102090.expedition: Hehe, it's about time we reap the rewards of that commission, Commander!
couple_encourage: Come on, fellow big sisters. Let's work hard together!
"Hao" do you do, folks?
102090.mail: Some new mail just arrived. You sure are popular, Commander!
102090.feeling3: Mm... I'm not trying to make myself look stronger than I am or anything, but honestly, I think there aren't many people like you who I can speak to like an equal...

301290.detail: Houshou's carrot cake is just divine! I hope to taste it again sometime.
301290.touch: Huh? Have I done something incorrectly?
301290.login: Commander, you're not the type to dilly-dally around, are you? That makes two of us! We'd better begin our work for the day!
301290.battle: Shall I assume command? Understood! I won't disappoint you!
301290.hp_warning: Don't die on me now, engines... Please hang in there!
301290.feeling2: I am THE strongest destroyer! Or, so I'd like to think. But to truly become the strongest, I'll have to hone myself through my training and sorties!
301290.headtouch: Mweeehhh... Please, d-don't touch my ears! It makes me shooo weak... Aaaahh...
301290.mission_complete: Mission completed! Quick, let's check what rewards we've earned!
301290.main: My rigging calibration checks out. I'm fully prepared to sortie at your command!|My shoes? They're quite special. In fact, these shoes are what allow me to go faster than everyone else! Ha-hah!|The Sakura Empire is home to many sword-wielding shipgirls... If I ever get the chance, I'd love to borrow and swing someone else's sword for myself.|Any two people can come to an understanding as long they're both willing to listen! That's what I've always believed!
301290.feeling5: Could we go somewhere together after finishing our work today? B-because, well, we hardly get any time for ourselves during office hours... Okay, look! I'm saying I want some alone time with you, Commander! Would you... oblige?
301290.upgrade: I can become even faster... even stronger!
301290.unlock: I am Shimakaze, the world's one and only Shimakaze-class destroyer! You must be the commander! Let us join forces and work towards our goals, together!
301290.feeling4: Commander, what things motivate you to keep fighting? I'm just asking out of curiosity. Whatever they are, I will fight for them alongside you! ...Yes, I know, I swear not to get ahead of myself this time!
301290.feeling1: If you manage to right all your wrongs, then maybe you'll earn my forgiveness!
301290.propose: What is THIS?! Wasn't this meant to be an emergency mission briefing?! Wait, what's this ring...? I fell for it, hook, line, and sinker! But why trick me into coming? I would've agreed to it if you'd just told the truth!
301290.skill: Maybe I should turn this into one of my secret moves!
301290.profile: I'm Shimakaze, the sole Shimakaze-class destroyer! I boast the highest speed and best torpedo capabilities of all fleet destroyers – a pivotal part of any torpedo squadron! No type of operation is beyond my capabilities! Ha-hah!
301290.touch2: Eek! What has gotten into you?! If I didn't know any better, I'd think... Well, just this once, I'll turn a blind eye to it.
301290.mission: Aha! I spy with my little eye incomplete missions! Full speed ahead for those rewards! Right, Commander?
301290.home: W-welcome back, Commander! ...No, it's nothing, really! I was just wondering when you'd return...
301290.expedition: Hmm... Commission teams don't run into ambushes out at sea, do they...?
couple_encourage: You can go faster than me？Really?!
Let's rush them down!
Is Planet Bunny a real place?! I must know!
I'll scout ahead, Suruga!
I'm... a starter ship, too? That's weird, because I don't really feel like one...
Takao! Do you think better of me now?
L-Lady Nagato?! I-i-it's an honor fighting alongside you!
301290.mail: Apropos of nothing, I think you should check your latest mail.
301290.feeling3: People often say I'm too hasty, but isn't swift decision-making supposed to be a good thing? Plus, if you don't fight with all you've got, it could come back to haunt you! Hehehe!

304021.detail: Which pillow would you prefer? The soft one, the hard one, or... perhaps you'd like to use my thighs? Hehe~
304021.touch: Commander, the moon is beautiful tonight. Wouldn't you rather take in the beauty of the night sky instead of staring at me?
304021.login: Adequate rest is important for improving your performance. Commander, I've prepared your pillow. Tonight... enjoy the best sleep of your life~
304021.main: Hehe, it seems like we'll be able to have a pajama party banquet. How about it, Commander? Would you like to join? |Good night, Commander. Don't worry, I'll wake you up when the time is right. |Ah, the plum blossoms shimmering under the moonlight... Commander, shall we go watch the petals together?
304021.unlock: Look how late it is... Commander, shall we embark on a dreamy voyage together?
304021.drop_descrip: Look how late it is... Commander, shall we embark on a dreamy voyage together?
304021.touch2: Hehe~ Someone seems quite energetic tonight, Commander.

202180.detail: To perform a curtsy, a lady puts her feet across each other like— Forgive me, I failed to do it...
202180.touch: Master, you'll end up a failure if you rely on others too often. Sometimes, you must— Mmh, you leave me no choice. I-I won't help you next time, okay...?
202180.login: Master, would you like some tea?
202180.battle: It's a maid's duty to remove her Master's obstacles!
202180.hp_warning: Master, perhaps it would be a good idea to retreat...?
202180.feeling2: There are so many ships here... Master, does "commander" refer to an incredibly wealthy person who owns a shipyard?
202180.mission_complete: The mission rewards are here. If I prove to be of service to you, will I receive rewards too?
202180.main: You'd like whiskey and coffee... Umm, d-do you not drink tea...?|Master, is there anything you would like me to do?|Master, neglecting your commander duties is a big no-no!
202180.feeling5: Master, do you think I will be a lady worthy of you, when I grow up?
202180.upgrade: I'm not quite used to fighting, but please have faith in me.
202180.unlock: My Master is also a commander... Umm, so the commander is a captain of a ship? I don't quite understand, but... I will stay here for a while if you don't mind. I am Belfast, maid-in-training. It is a pleasure to serve you.
202180.feeling4: I now completely understand how you think, Master... Umm, is this what's known as "empathy"? No, perhaps it's just overly easy to understand you, Master...
202180.feeling1: You are more troublesome than a kitchen stain, Master.
202180.propose: Does this mean you "approve of me"? Thank you, Master. However... if I wear this ring, people may get the wrong idea about you... P-perhaps you should think this through more thoroughly?
202180.skill: Dear enemies, this is going to be a liiiittle bit painful.
202180.profile: I am Belfast, born in Harland and Wolff. Yes, the same place as the Titanic. I actually have an older sister. She hasn't taken care of me very much, however... Umm, that's all I was going to say. Master, what type of person are you?
202180.touch2: Don't worry, Master. Even if you go to prison, I will still bring you your meals.
202180.mission: Master, should you really let all these mission documents pile up...?
202180.home: Are you hungry, Master? I'm feeling quite peckish. Shall we eat together?
202180.win_mvp: This isn't... anything to brag about. Isn't that right, Master?
202180.expedition: Master, the ladies have returned from their commission and are waiting for you.
202180.mail: Master, would you like me to leave this letter here...?
202180.feeling3: Do I feel nervous? Well, Master is a nice person, and none of the ladies here are merchant ships, so I have nothing to be nervous about.
202180.lose: A lady must be elegant, even in defeat... *Sob*...

408022.detail: Another sortie? I'll be right out. ...It's fine, I can go dressed like this.
408022.touch: Here's to you, for taking good care of me.
408022.main: I'm a little more talkative now? Huh... I just find I have more to talk about with you.|The party...? I wouldn't know what to do with myself out there.|I'm always stuck with a bunch of noisy girls: U-73, U-81, U-101... But even though I like it quiet, I really don't mind them that much.
408022.feeling5: It's nice to be left alone, but the feeling I get when I'm with you... it feels almost addictive.
408022.unlock: Sigh... I'd much rather be in a nice, quiet place like this over the din and clamor of the venue... Wouldn't you agree, Commander? I see. Well, come sit here then.
408022.drop_descrip: Sigh... I'd much rather be in a nice, quiet place like this over the din and clamor of the venue... Wouldn't you agree, Commander? I see. Well, come sit here then.
408022.home: They're looking for me? Tell them to stop worrying. I'm fine.

301112.drop_descrip: Inazuma and I have been to a lot of festivals together, but this would be the first time that I've gone with you, Commander. Isn't this totally like a date?

202172.detail: Akashi said she'd give me this bike in exchange for some "marketing." Sooo... Boss, what do you think? Wanna buy one?
202172.touch: Do you hear it, boss? The rumbling of her engine? She thirsts for the open road. What are you waiting for? Hop on! But don't forget your helmet.
202172.main: This baby's got more horsepower than the other one, even if it's less reliable. She's still a good bike.|Worried about your hair? Well, safety's the most important thing on the road, so you'd better hang on to this helmet.|Boss, would you like to learn about motorcycles? I thought you might. Let's begin with starting the engine. First...
202172.feeling5: I once thought myself a traveler, with nothing to tie me down, with no real destination... Turns out I was wrong, Boss. I'll always come back to you, no matter what happens.
202172.unlock: Look, Boss, this is the new bike that Akashi sent me. She said she wanted me to be her brand ambassador... Doesn't that job sound badass?
202172.drop_descrip: Look, Boss, this is the new bike that Akashi sent me. She said she wanted me to be her brand ambassador... Doesn't that job sound badass?
202172.home: Boss, the mountains are lovely this time of year. How about it?

108061.detail: Albacore's been teasing you? Give me specifics, so I know what to do for future reference... Err, so we can work out a way to deny her, I mean! Yeah, that's it!
108061.touch: Hm? Got something on your mind? Just say it, I promise I won't poke fun of you for it~
108061.login: Welcome to a paradise of relaxation and recreation! Where you can get skip a little work and nobody'll find out~
108061.main: What happens when you give a Meowfficer bunny ears? It gets promoted to a hare admiral! Hahaha~|Shinano's not coming? That sucks. I already mixed a special cocktail for her and everything!|You deserve a super special reward for all your hard work, Commander~ What kind of reward? Hahaha~ Well, what do you want?
108061.unlock: You're our lucky guest today, Commander~ You get a taste of my secret concoction... Excuse me, I meant to say "cocktail!" Relax, it won't do anything weird to you~ Probably. Ahaha~
108061.drop_descrip: You're our lucky guest today, Commander~ You get a taste of my secret concoction... Excuse me, I meant to say "cocktail!" Relax, it won't do anything weird to you~ Probably. Ahaha~
108061.touch2: Don't you start making excuses now! The drinks I served you were alcohol-free!
108061.home: What's this drink... "Bluest Blue?" Ah. The name alone makes it obvious Bluegill came up with it. It's just carbonated water on the rocks.

213040.detail: It's so much fun to fire my gun~!

213040.login: That loud bang? Tee hee~ You were gone for so long I was getting bored, so I let a shot loose~
213040.battle: Tee hee, what should I knock out first? Their bow? Turret? Engine?
213040.feeling2: Tee hee~ How do you like my habanero curry? – Huh...? W-wait, Nelson! I didn't know that one was yours! – Don't hurt meeee!
213040.mission_complete: Commander, is the next mission gonna be as fun as the last one?
213040.main: My hobby's collecting shell casings~! Hey, don't you think shell casings are super cool?|Top of the mornin', granny Hood!|Whuaah! Hey, Wales! Granny Hood is giving me creepy looks~!
213040.feeling5: I wonder if I can combine you and my Mark I... Commander, for the next sortie, how about you sit atop it while issuing commands?
213040.upgrade: Tee hee~ I might be loading a teensy bit too much gunpowder~
213040.unlock: Take THIS! – Oh, Commander? Tee hee~ I'm Abercrombie! Lovely weather today, eh~?
213040.feeling4: Feeling stressed out? Then try out my Mark I! Fire a shot for every worry you have to make them disappear with a bang! You'll get hooked on it!
213040.feeling1: Tee hee~ Commander, did you know you can use the Mark I as a blunt weapon? I'll show you! (Pow!)
213040.propose: W-wow! Thanks! I'll never take it off! I-in exchange, take my Mark I! Roberts told me you're supposed to give your partner your dearest possession at times like these!
213040.skill: Be torn to shreds by my shells!
213040.profile: I'm the Monitor Abercrombie. My sister and I used to help with shore bombardment around the Mediterranean Sea. Tee hee~ It's way more fun to shoot stationary targets~
213040.mission: Commander, there are new missions! Tee hee~ What'll we be sinking this time? I can't wait~
213040.home: Hey, Commander~ Brought back anything gander-worthy? Like a piece of wreckage or parts from a crashed aircraft or something?
213040.win_mvp: Kaboom! Ahaha~ You can't beat the Mark I!
213040.expedition: Target spotted, calculating trajectory... Bugger, it's just the commission team. Laaaame...
couple_encourage: Auntie Hood, I'm here to help!
Nobody can pull off pranks better than me!
213040.mail: Oh, have I hidden your mail~? Want it back? Then get some snacks and bar-ter for it! Bar-ter for it!
213040.feeling3: Oh, Commander~! Com-man-der! Coooommaaaandeeeer! What? It was nothing. I just wanted to see your face~ Tee hee~

101254.detail: Wh-what do you think?! Like I'd ever agree to be turned into a present! It's just... I didn't know what else to give you for Christmas...
101254.touch: G-give me some space, you idiot! ...N-no, that doesn't mean I'm telling you to stay away!
101254.login: I'll do it myself! Hngghh! *pant*... I-I can't do it after all... Stop being useless and help me out!
101254.battle: Finally, I'm free again... Now you're going to feel my wrath!
101254.main: Just how long are you gonna keep me like this, you half-witted commander?!|Hmph! You're not gonna get any work done without me helping you!|I haven't given Yorktown my present yet... I can't just be stuck like this all day!
101254.unlock: I-I'm nobody's surprise! Ugh, I should've never listened to Sims... Stop staring already and undo these ribbons around my arms!
101254.drop_descrip: I-I'm nobody's surprise! Ugh, I should've never listened to Sims... Stop staring already and undo these ribbons around my arms!
101254.touch2: You're really exploiting the fact that I can't move... I'm never, ever forgiving you for this!
101254.home: Do you think it's funny to leave me stuck in this box?!

307071.detail: Oh, how I envy you, kitty. If I were you, my Commander could hold me tight and never let go.
307071.touch: My Commander, how would you like to go for a stroll somewhere private?
307071.login: I've been waiting for you, my Commander.
