307071.unlock: You're taking so long to dress yourself, my Commander. Are you struggling to find something to match my dress? Hehe, it doesn't matter what you wear, you're always perfect to me♡
307071.drop_descrip: You're taking so long to dress yourself, my Commander. Are you struggling to find something to match my dress? Hehe, it doesn't matter what you wear, you're always perfect to me♡
307071.touch2: Yesss, that's it, my Commander, give all your love and attention to Taihou alone...
307071.home: My Commander, let me clean up the few remaining insects troubling you.
307071.win_mvp: This is what happens when you get between me and my Commander!

303091.detail: "There's no need to overexert yourself." That's what Myoukou told me, anyway. Commander, hopefully you're not pushing yourself too hard?
303091.login: You'd like to train with me? Of course! Even dressed like this, I have no intention of losing!
303091.battle: My appearances shouldn't affect my combat performance... In any case, let's advance!
303091.main: It's hard to put my hair up like this... Thanks to Myoukou's help, I was somehow able to manage... |I can't sit here doing nothing all the time... Commander, if there's anything you need help with, please give me the order! |This is how you do the lap pillow thing, right? I heard that it would help you recover from fatigue...
303091.unlock: Phew... I finally managed to fix my dress... but I just can't seem to get used to it. Commander, how does my dress look? It's not strange, is it?
303091.drop_descrip: Phew... I finally managed to fix my dress... but I just can't seem to get used to it. Commander, how does my dress look? It's not strange, is it?
303091.touch2: Umm... C-Commander, Myoukou said that you shouldn't do stuff like this...
303091.home: Phew... Let's take a break, Commander.

603020.detail: Now, Pola and I are often praised for our beauty, but aren't you worried that all this ogling might cause some unsavory rumors?
603020.touch: You like my sword, Commander? Or could it be... something else you're interested in?
603020.login: Welcome back. I've gathered everyone up and we're awaiting your inspection.
603020.battle: I'm used to being flagship. All ships, get into formation! Tiro!
603020.feeling2: Is there something bothering you, Commander? Let's hear it then.
603020.mission_complete: Mission complete! My my, that's quite a big reward there, isn't it? Well done, Commander~
603020.main: Tenacemente, that is, fighting to the bitter end, no matter the odds, is my personal motto.|Looking up at the night sky, admiring the countless glimmering stars, it's really nice, actually. But it's better enjoyed from inside... don't you think?|By the way, I've actually got kind of an eye for fashion. How about I help dress you next time, Commander?
603020.feeling5: Commander, after all this time together, you should already know what I'm thinking before I even open my mouth. Hehe, so who am I thinking about right now? Of course it's you, Commander, that's too easy. Hehehe♪
603020.upgrade: Grazie! Now my main guns are an even greater threat to the enemy.
603020.unlock: Ciao. It's a pleasure to meet you, Commander. I'm the heavy cruiser, Zara, and I look forward to bringing victory and glory to your fleet.
603020.feeling4: Now that we're finally alone together, was there something you wanted to do, Commander? ... You want me to clean your ears? Well, all right... Come, put your head right here~ And please, try to relax, okay? I'm going to very gently, very slowly, clean your ears♪
603020.feeling1: Terrible... There's absolutely nothing about this commander anyone could ever find appealing...
603020.propose: You really think you can bind me to you with nothing but a cheap little ring? This isn't nearly enough~ ... Hehe, don't give me that face... Haha, I'm only joking~ Don't worry, Commander. I'll be with you forever.
603020.skill: Don't think you can pierce my armor so easily!
603020.profile: I am the first ship of the Zara class of heavy cruisers, Zara. I was born to be a marine battery, with my magnificent guns and armor plating. I served as the flagship of my squadron, at least until that fateful night...
603020.touch2: Eeek?! ... Ahem! There is more to me than my armor plating, you know? Maybe you would like a taste of my guns as well?
603020.mission: Is this mission giving you trouble? Here, let me take a look.
603020.home: An exhausting mission, was it? Why not relax with a glass of wine?
603020.win_mvp: I've brought you victory and glory, just as I promised.
603020.expedition: Commander, you must profusely thank all these girls for ensuring the safe delivery of these supplies.
couple_encourage: We're allies now, huh... I'm counting on your fire support then!
603020.mail: Commander? The mail is here. If you don't get to it soon, I could always read it out loud for you? I wonder if there are any love letters, hehehe...
603020.feeling3: Despite her appearances, Pola is a really sensitive girl, you know? And anyone who dares to hurt her... even you, Commander, would not be easily forgiven.
603020.lose: Ugh... Don't make me recall the humiliation I endured that night...!

301113.detail: Commander! If you get the Inazuma DLC, you'll have a full set of wings!
301113.touch: How am I supposed to fly with only one wing? ...Well, even if I had two, it probably still wouldn't work out!
301113.login: Commander, finally decided to "log in," huh? Wanna join the party?
301113.main: I've brought a bunch of mouth-watering strawberries! Commander, wanna try one?|We thought Akatsuki had gotten lost again, but Hibiki seems to have bumped into her. I see, I see, so that's what we call a "random encounter!"|Don't you think this tooty manjuu is a bit annoying? ...You don't even see it, Commander?
301113.unlock: I'm the fairy of thunder that shatters the night to herald the dawn! I see, I see! That is a good backstory! Commander, want to head to the party together?
301113.drop_descrip: I'm the fairy of thunder that shatters the night to herald the dawn! I see, I see! That is a good backstory! Commander, want to head to the party together?
301113.home: Going straight from grinding EXP to grinding at the party, huh? I'd expect nothing less of you, Commander!

605022.detail: As proud as we are of our wonderful Sardegnian thermae, and as befittingly charming it is when Veneto conducts foreign relations from them, the fact remains that diplomacy should be left to the pros. Wouldn't you agree?
605022.touch: To be frank, I've been to so many parties that I've grown a bit tired of them. Let's do something interesting for a change, shall we, Commander?
605022.login: None but you are permitted to keep me waiting, Commander.
605022.main: Now, who will be the lucky recipient of Littorio's rose this time? Oh, but of course, Commander. If you want it, maybe you'll get it?|There are two kinds of parties in the world: those with Littorio in attendance, and those without.|I personally picked out all the various furnishings in here. It is no exaggeration to call this suite "La Littorio" itself. How do you like the sound of that, Commander?
605022.feeling5: Commander... you are an unlabeled bottle of fine riserva with more charm than meets the eye – your taste enchanting, maddening, and making one possessive over you. And I – Littorio – am no exception, tesoro mio.
605022.unlock: Welcome to Littorio's personal suite. Are you here to issue me a challenge of who can romance the most girls? Hahahah, I'm joking of course! There'd be no fun in a game I would win every single time.
605022.drop_descrip: Welcome to Littorio's personal suite. Are you here to issue me a challenge of who can romance the most girls? Hahahah, I'm joking of course! There'd be no fun in a game I would win every single time.
605022.home: Let us have a grand toast to the triumphant return of our hero. Alla salute!

202153.detail: The operas are just a glimpse of the Dragon Empery's five thousand rich years of culture and history... As a ship with a deep connection with the Dragon Empery, I hope to share the charm of these ancient traditions with many more people!
202153.touch: What are these weapons for? Um, right now, I mostly play the flower girl character, but I hope to be able to play some warriors too! Hehe~
202153.login: What kind of performance should I prepare for today? I have too many things to choose from...
202153.main: One of the specialities of Sichuan opera is something called "mask changing." It lets you quickly portray different emotions, or even different characters. Hehe, it took a lot of practice to be able to do this. |"Behind each minute on the stage is ten years of practice." The Dragon Empery's old adages are quite thought-provoking... |Commander, do you know how many different types of plays there are in the Dragon Empery?
202153.feeling5: Commander, is there some mask that represents... um, "love?" Huh? Just show it with my own face? G-goodness, Commander, an elegant lady is supposed to maintain her composure.
202153.unlock: "Next, Aurora will perform something you've never seen before - traditional Sichuan mask-changing opera!" Hehe... Commander, I look like the real deal, right?
202153.drop_descrip: "Next, Aurora will perform something you've never seen before - traditional Sichuan mask-changing opera!" Hehe... Commander, I look like the real deal, right?
202153.touch2: C-Commander?! If you keep this up, I'm going to use my polearm and sword, and um... it's going to hurt!
202153.home: Commander, you must be tired. Ahem! Please have some refreshments while you enjoy my upcoming performance!

301540.detail: Ugh... C-could you please not stare so much...?
301540.touch: Hoppy is cute, isn't he? Ehehe~ He's always there with me when I go to bed.
301540.login: Welcome back, Commander... Come on, Hoppy, say hi to the Commander.
301540.battle: I-I'm supposed to give orders?! ... Whuah?! C-come on, everyone!
301540.hp_warning: I-I'm not going to give up!
301540.feeling2: Why do I like to hide behind you...? Umm, that's because... I feel more comfortable with you leading the way, Commander...
301540.mission_complete: A mission... Yes, it seems a mission has been completed! You're quite the go-getter, Commander...
301540.main: I feel safe around Yuugure. I enjoy playing and having sleepovers with her. I wish I had more friends like her...|Oh no, a-another air raid?! ... Commander, please don't scare me like that!|I'm always doing my best, trying to catch up to everyone... S-so please, don't ever leave me behind, okay...?
301540.feeling5: I'm not scared of the dark or planes when I'm with you, Commander... W-would you mind if, from now on, I walked ahead of you, rather than behind you...?
301540.upgrade: Hoppy and I think we got a little stronger...
301540.unlock: Yuugumo-class destroyer Kiyonami, r-reporting for duty... And this is my friend, Hoppy... I-it's nice to meet you! ... Ugh...
301540.feeling4: I have many more fluffy friends than just Hoppy... Commander, would you like to come visit my House of Fluffs sometime later...?
301540.feeling1: Everyone's been saying the Commander is a mean person... Commander, is that really true...?
301540.propose: Will we really be able to be together forever from now on...? That's great...! N-now, I learned from Yuugure that... the next thing I should do is close my eyes and wait for you to do something, right? O-okay!
301540.skill: W-we will do this together, Hoppy!
301540.profile: I'm Kiyonami, the eighth Yuugumo-class destroyer... I had improved anti-air capabilities, but neither Yuugure nor I could really deal with things in the air... Ugh... If only I'd done a better job back then... B-but even so, I did achieve a couple of things! Wh-what I'm getting at is that I'll do the best job I can...!
301540.touch2: I-I'm not sure why you're doing this... B-but please stop, it tickles, Commander...!
301540.mission: We still have quite a few missions to complete... Commander, can you do it...?
301540.home: Well done on the last sortie, Commander... W-would you like to pet Hoppy? I-it's really comforting to stroke his fluffy fur...
301540.win_mvp: I-I got... first place? Y-you're... not just joking, right...?
301540.expedition: The commission team just returned to port. Umm... I think we should go check on them...
couple_encourage: Yuugure, d-do you mind if I stay behind you...?
301540.mail: Your mail has arrived! Let's take a look at it, Commander!
301540.feeling3: Ugh... It's so scary at night... Commander, w-when it gets late, could you pretty please lead me to the dorm...?

307070.detail: I belong to you, my Commander, body and soul...
307070.login: Would you like to take a bath with me? Maybe you'd like to taste me? Orrr~ would you like to do it with me...? Ahahaha!
307070.battle: I'll tear down everything and everyone that stands between me and my Commander! AHAHAHAHA!
307070.hp_warning: For my Commander, I have to win...!
307070.feeling2: I know everything, EVERYTHING there is to know about you, my Commander~ In fact, my Commander is my entire world.
307070.mission_complete: Mission complete~ Want to go get the rewards?
307070.main: Hehehe, I would pull the moon from the sky for you, if you wanted it, my Commander.|You like small ones, my Commander? Then I'm off to cull the big ones, hehehe...|My Commander, you know you can never EVER lie to me. Or else...
307070.feeling5: The bed and toiletries in your quarters? Of course they're mine. I should have thought of this before~ If you don't want me going in and out of your room all the time, we should just be sleeping together. Hehehe... please be gentle with me.
307070.upgrade: Ahaha, now I can serve my Commander even better...
307070.unlock: This heat, and this throbbing... We meet at last, my dear Commander! I am Taihou, unworthy as I am, at your service♡
307070.feeling4: You forgot your coat? Well isn't my Commander forgetful... Don't worry about it, I'll go get your coat for you. Huh? The key to your quarters? Hehehe, you can keep it. Taihou has her ways.
307070.feeling1: Those insects... Just a second, my Commander, I need to do something about these impudent little insects...
307070.propose: It's finally on my finger! You know, I would have thrown this ring out long ago if it didn't have my name on it. Hehehe. Oh? How did I know about it? I tollld you, I know EVERYTHING about my Commander. And from now on I'm going to love EVERYTHING about you too~
307070.skill: Now you can die happy, ahaha...
307070.profile: I'm a state-of-the-art aircraft carrier with extra reinforced armor. Just look at my flight deck and enclosed hangar. Amazing, aren't they? Hmm? What's this about carrying capacity and firefighting systems? Never mind that... Tell me, what do you think of my... body?
307070.touch2: If you touch any other girls like this, I might have to punish you, my Commander.
307070.mission: There's a new mission. Can we go?
307070.home: Mission accomplished! And let me say how fantastic you looked on the battlefield.
307070.win_mvp: I dedicate this victory to my Commander!
307070.expedition: Commission complete... But if you ordered it, my Commander, I would clear all of them for you... I must mean so much to my Commander.
307070.mail: My Commander, you've got mail~ I licked it very tho-rough-ly. It's safe.
307070.feeling3: ... That gift she gave you? Oh, I threw that out. Why wouldn't I? Only my things belong on your desk~
307070.lose: Why aren't you dead... why won't you all just DIE?!

605021.detail: Veneto? Don't expect much from her... No, I don't mean her swimsuit. She's the type that would spend the entire day building a sand Colosseum.
605021.touch: Donning swimwear to display one's glamor for all to see – isn't it fantastic, Commander?
605021.login: I see you've returned, Commander. Hmph, today my glory shines brighter than even the sun.

Which one are you, Commander?|The Mediterranean Sea is thing of beauty in summer, but this sea surpasses it in sheer bustle. I prefer this one; it lets my glamor reach the hearts and minds of many more.|What? That damned Veneto is going to play beach volleyball?! ... I must help her, to ensure the Sardegna Empire's glory remains unsullied...
605021.unlock: A visit to the beach with me? Then you must try your hardest to stand out. Otherwise the eyes of the world will be on me alone.
605021.drop_descrip: A visit to the beach with me? Then you must try your hardest to stand out. Otherwise the eyes of the world will be on me alone.
605021.home: Heheh, I say you deserve some "eye candy." Interested, Commander?

303092.detail: I originally planned to bring headphones to listen to the soothing sound of Myoukou's... Err, I meant to say music! But, it might be more calming to just listen to the waves.
303092.touch: Commander, did you want to take a break? ...Ahem! H-h-how about a l-l-lap pillow?
303092.login: The cool, pristine waves splashing across my skin... What a comforting sensation.

303092.drop_descrip: This whole "fashion coordination" concept is still a bit hard for me to wrap my head around, so I'm glad Nachi helped me pick out a swimsuit. Now, I just need to... Hey, Commander! Open your mouth! H-huh?! But this is what Nachi told me to do... is there some sort of problem?!
303092.touch2: Eep?! ...Oh, I had cream stuck on me? Th-thank you, Commander...
303092.home: I heard there are lots of crabs hiding on this beach. I wonder if I can snag a couple...

107111.detail: Nice catch! You've got skill! How about becoming my catcher?

107111.login: It's not enough to just be a pitcher. I've gotta be a good batter as well! Oh, Bluegill's also out there training. Let's grab her for our practice!
107111.main: A ponytail really does get in the way, huh... Next time, maybe I'll try putting it up... |Gah! I threw the ball full power and lost control of it... My bad, my bad! |All righty! This one's headed towards the ends of the universe! Wait, how's the catcher gonna get it then...

107111.drop_descrip: There's been a lot of inter-port meets recently... But before I can join a team with my other Eagle Union colleagues, I've got to up my game first! So, Commander, mind training with me?
107111.touch2: Even if you brought protection, getting hit by my fastball is gonna hurt like hell~
107111.home: Phew, time for a break! Commander, thanks for coming out with me! Feel free to use the equipment however you'd like!
107111.win_mvp: Nobody can return one of my pitches!
107111.lose: Gah, I gave up a run...

304031.detail: I think people will gawk at us if Kirishima and I walk around looking like this... *Sigh*... It's tough being popular...
304031.touch: I always look forward to the lunch box Hiei makes for me every day.
304031.battle: Shoot... No time... Let's finish them, quick!

304031.unlock: I think it's fine to enjoy school life once in a while... Hm? You wanna know what I'm listening to? Sure, if you're okay with just one earbud.
304031.drop_descrip: I think it's fine to enjoy school life once in a while... Hm? You wanna know what I'm listening to? Sure, if you're okay with just one earbud.
304031.touch2: ... Do you want me to beat you over the head with my bag?

202140.detail: Geez~ If you keep on looking at me like that, I'll be reporting you to the authorities~
202140.touch: Hehe~ Commander, you really like to engage in skinship, don't you? Well, just this once, I'm allowing you to continue a bit more~
202140.login: I'm going to do this and that again today. Please take care of it~
202140.battle: Such disobedient kids~~ They must be punished~
202140.feeling2: It takes a long time for the bond to form after you tie the red string of fate. Do try hard, Commander~
202140.mission_complete: I'm gonna take your share of the rewards too, Commander.
202140.main: Commander, I'm wearing new clothes today! --Hmm? I didn't say I'm heading out!|Commander, are you free? How about taking a walk together? I want to link our arms and be seen by the other girls|Hmm? Did you not hear that? ...There's no helping it. Lie down over here and let me check your ears
202140.feeling5: The red string of fate was what made me grow from a seed, and you, Commander, were the one who made me bloom~ You're so great~ *kiss*
202140.unlock: I am Galatea, the 2nd of the Arethusa class~ Do you believe in fate, Commander? It is fate that I meet with you~
202140.feeling4: Commander, let me have your ear... *kiss*. I like you~ ... Yep. Such a thing would have to be done in reality, right~
202140.feeling1: Do you understand? Even the red string of fate is not absolute. I no longer think about anything concerning you anymore, Commander~
202140.propose: With this, the bond of fate has been formed~ There's still a long way ahead of us, so let's take care of each other, darling~
202140.drop_descrip: Arethusa-class light cruiser – Galatea, Hull Number 71!
202140.skill: This has nothing to do with my fate~
202140.profile: I am Galatea, the second ship of the Arethusa class. I may not look like it, but in my service in the Mediterranean, I achieved some results~ You'll regret it if you underestimate me~
202140.touch2: Ah... You're daring, Commander --Well then, do you want to hear my wishes?
202140.mission: Yes, let's see what today's missions are about~
202140.home: Aaaah cease your attacks! I'm on your side!
202140.win_mvp: You cannot escape from me! Be good, and accept~ your~ punishment~
202140.expedition: Commander~ *arms folded* let's head to the docks and greet the girls who went off for commissions
202140.mail: Mail time~ I wonder what reward I'll get for bringing it to you~?
202140.feeling3: I like you Commander, but it's important for all of us to be together. I'm troubled~
202140.lose: Hmph! ...I curse you to be destroyed by my allies!

202130.detail: ...Idiot! Did no one teach you that it's rude to stare at a girl?!
202130.touch: I-it's not like I'm fond of being touched by an idiot like you! ...I just feel sorry for you since you're so lonely!
202130.login: Commander, I'm gonna get angry if you don't take this seriously!
202130.battle: Listen up! Our pride rides on this battle! Let's take this seriously!
202130.feeling2: I do not acknowledge a Commander like you! Hmph!
202130.mission_complete: Doesn't the reward suit you just fine? Hurry up and get it!
202130.main: Even if they are allies, I will not show mercy to any threat towards  my comrades!|...Leaving me alone like this... I-I'm not feeling lonely or anything!|Hmph! You suck, Commander, so stop making me worry about you!
202130.feeling5: Umm... Good work... I mean, it's nothing! I just made some snacks since I felt like it, so hurry up and eat them!
202130.upgrade: Commander, don't get in my way!
202130.unlock: You can be at ease now that I, Arethusa, have come. If anything, Commander, don't you dare become my hindrance!
202130.feeling4: You do have some positive qualities... Hmph! My opinion of you is slightly improved! There's still a lot for you to do!
202130.feeling1: I cannot acknowledge a commander like you!
202130.propose: You dummy. You're making this too formal! This... should've been done a while ago...
202130.drop_descrip: Arethusa-class light cruiser – Arethusa, Hull Number 26!
202130.skill: If we keep doing this dillgently, it will all work out!
202130.profile: I am the Arethusa class treaty cruiser, Arethusa: the first cruiser in the world designed with vertical armor! --Hmph! The fact that I'm amazing was decided from the beginning!
202130.touch2: Aaah! Pervert! Molester! Lewd! Go and die!
202130.mission: Idiot! Stop sleeping! There's a new mission!
202130.home: You're so lacking at work that you're only good at returning here!
202130.win_mvp: Hmph! I will not acknowledge you just because you complimented me!
202130.expedition: The commission team is back. Hurry up and check the results from them, you idiot!
202130.mail: It's your mail so hurry up and get it. ...It's not like I'm concerned about who it's from! Hmph!
202130.feeling3: Don't get carried away! I came here because of a tasty cake! It's still too early for me to acknowledge you!
202130.lose: Ugh... How could I fall here... of all places...

301541.detail: I'm not sure what wrapping paper to use for my presents... Ummhh... Could you help me pick out a good one, Commander...?
301541.touch: Sometimes... Hoppy is on his own, but we always go to bed together at night.
301541.login: M-Merry Christmas, Commander! Phew... I think I said that right!

Th-that includes you, of course, Commander!|All these warm lights at Christmas make me feel at ease... I wish it was Christmas all year round...
301541.unlock: S-sorry to keep you waiting... Yuugure and I picked out this outfit together. She said it "looked very Christmassy," but it doesn't look weird, right? ... Ugh...
301541.drop_descrip: S-sorry to keep you waiting... Yuugure and I picked out this outfit together. She said it "looked very Christmassy," but it doesn't look weird, right? ... Ugh...
301541.touch2: Y-you'll make my hood come undone... Ugh...
301541.home: Well done on the last sortie. W-would you like a snack? I have gingerbread cookies and Christmas cake...

705040.detail: If excellency is what you seek from the Sovetsky Soyuz class, I am your best and only true option!
705040.touch: Let me guess, you are simply poking me for your own amusement, and not because you need something done. Am I wrong?
705040.login: Aha! I knew you'd be back right at this hour, Comrade! Rossiya doubted my intuition.
705040.battle: Crush the enemy! Break their spirits, then their bones!
705040.hp_warning: The battle is still under our control!
705040.feeling2: How about a bet, Comrade? Do you think your job will only be accomplished thanks to my help, or regardless of it?
705040.headtouch: Your little hand gestures have no effect on me.
705040.mission_complete: Fantastic. With HQ's missions complete, we can finally continue with our own plan.
705040.main: It's much more entertaining to lure your foes into a trap one at a time than to crush them all at once. Am I right?|Seems it's all quiet on the western front... Don't you have any palpitating news?|There is no greater pleasure than decimating your enemy with minimal losses. Wouldn't you agree?
705040.feeling5: You don't mince your words, do you? I will say I do prefer a forthright confession of love over beating around the bush. Standing at the top of the world, gazing at the horizon, with you by my side – I like the sound of that. Ahahaha!
705040.upgrade: We will curb the enemy with our superior firepower! Hahaha!
705040.unlock: Comrade, are you sure you're ready to have me under your command? Very well! Let us join hands and lay waste to our enemies — using my methods, of course!
705040.feeling4: If you ever tire of managing the fleet and planning battles, I will take over for you. You can rest easy, knowing I will bring you good reports on the daily. Although, knowing your devotion to your job, I doubt you'd ever delegate it to get some rest.
705040.feeling1: I don't care. You are absolutely nothing to me. Just stay out of my way.
705040.propose: You hope this ring will forever connect me with you, do you? Then I believe it will, because I believe in you. Only you are capable of standing at the top of the world together with me. Do not let me down, Comrade.
705040.profile: My sisters and I were devised as part of Project 23, but we never saw the light of day, much less fought in the war... But on the other hand, it would've been ludicrous to sail into battle equipped with second-rate armaments. Now though, I would be content with just getting to perform at full capacity under your command, Comrade.
705040.touch2: You chose the most depraved of ways to prove you have guts, Comrade.
705040.mission: Comrade, sure we should not allow the glorious advance of our fleet to be delayed by such trifling missions.
705040.home: Do not be so lenient with the enemy next time, Comrade.
705040.win_mvp: This comes as no surprise. All I did was nudge those fools toward the annihilation they so desired.
705040.expedition: Interested in a bet, Comrade? Do you think the commission team has returned with bountiful rewards, or few at all?
couple_encourage: Dropped some screws? I'll gather them up for you!
705040.mail: A letter? I welcome correspondence, assuming it is an enthralling read.
705040.feeling3: Oh, so you don't mind losing a bet if it means you get my help? I see. Well, regardless, it doesn't matter who wins a bet made on the spur of the moment. Now, what do you need assistance with, Comrade?

307073.detail: Would my Commander like to race? I would be happy to take care of the other racers to make sure you win first place... Oh... But why not?
307073.touch: I am here just to model for you, my Commander~
307073.login: My Commander, would you like a picture of me? Oh, not for promotional purposes, just for your "personal use..." Hehehe♡
307073.main: I don't care about prideful things like which carrier group I'm in. 307073.drop_descrip: Do I make a nice race queen, my Commander...? Hehe. With these proportions, and my fantastic outfit~♡ The others couldn't hope to compare with me!
couple_encourage: Unlucky...? We won't be hearing that again!

202126.touch2: Everything has its time and place, Master.

304030.detail: I wish I was as popular as Kirishima... Well, kind of...
304030.touch: Do you like Hiei's handmade sweets, too?
304030.login: Nice weather today. We should head out so we don't miss our chance to enjoy it. Don't you agree, Commander?
304030.feeling2: Kongou, allow me to give you a shoulder massage.

304030.feeling5: Commander, could I please be your dance partner for the next banquet Hiei is hosting...?

304030.feeling1: I've lost all hope in you.

304030.drop_descrip: Kongou-class fast battleship number four – Haruna.
304030.profile: I'm Haruna, the Sakura Empire's speediest fast battleship. I fought hard till the very end. Once more, I will fight with all my heart, holding nothing back!
304030.touch2: Hah!!!... I'll keep my gloves on next time so I can strike you without getting my hands dirty.
304030.mission: Hiei, what do you say we get some exercise?
304030.home: Well done out there. Did you run into any enemies?
304030.expedition: All right, I should head out and... Huh...? Not yet...?
couple_encourage: Kongou, am I doing well?!
All those before us... will fall!
Bear witness to my bravery!
Kure Battleship Fleet, charge!
304030.mail: I like your voice, Commander. So... could you read this letter out loud for me?
304030.feeling3: After a tough battle, I feel like eating a whole bucket full of rice.
304030.lose: Gah... I'm sorry, but... a loss is a loss...

202122.detail: It is only by maintaining a well-regulated lifestyle that one may keep a cool head and act appropriately when backed into a corner... It is with this in mind that I, Belfast, serve my Master as a maid.
202122.touch: Do let us know if you have any needs that the Royal Maids might service.
202122.login: Welcome home, Master. Your coffee is ready. Please, enjoy it at your leisure.
202122.main: Madam Enterprise's cooking has improved noticeably. 202122.upgrade: This power, it certainly is not just for the sake of destruction.

202122.drop_descrip: This is special cold-weather equipment inspired by Eagle Union designs. It was made for practical purposes such as special operations in frigid climates, and as such, was not designed with appearances in mind. Please do forgive me, Master.

202112.drop_descrip: Ahem! I made this special candy just for Halloween! Here, Commander, take some! Wooaaooah! Wh-who put this pumpkin here? It, it was me?!

202111.detail: Hmm...this Alchemy is really mysterious, but once I mastered it, then Belfast’s trust fund will...
202111.touch: Commander, wanna try my snacks? Ah~~
202111.login: This pendant is so cute, right?! I copied from that girl. Let's call her “Belfast”.
202111.battle: Tsk tsk, we don’t need her here. In any case, Belfast will always be by my side. Fleet, prepare for interception!
202111.main: Belfast, wake me up before you wake up Elizabeth. Otherwise, she will criticize me for getting up late again... |Do I look like a child who’s so easily bullied? Hehe, but as elegant as I am, no wonder I am called a fairy. |Victory, let me rub your cheeks again, doing so always brings me good luck.
202111.unlock: Why doesn't she have to go to school with me...she says she’s a maid for the Queen? Well, me too! You can be a maid and school girl at the same time...tsk tsk---
202111.drop_descrip: Why doesn't she have to go to school with me...she says she’s a maid for the Queen? Well, me too! You can be a maid and school girl at the same time...tsk tsk---

202111.expedition: Belfast, before you go to greet the girls returning from commission, could you brush my hair? It's a mess...

202101.detail: It was a terrible mistake letting Fiji handle this festival costuming... "Spice up this bit and the Commander'll love it," and such. It's all a game to that girl...

202101.login: Master, how is your work coming along? Let's avoid having you at the office for the holiday.

202101.unlock: Gloucester, light cruiser of the Royal Maids, at your service for the Spring Festival... You say I look displeased? I beg your pardon, it's just... Such holidays are in fact quite busy for the Maids. We have much on our minds. It is none of your concern.
202101.drop_descrip: Gloucester, light cruiser of the Royal Maids, at your service for the Spring Festival... You say I look displeased? I beg your pardon, it's just... Such holidays are in fact quite busy for the Maids. We have much on our minds. It is none of your concern.

102091.touch: Do you wanna try some of the pumpkin pie that Helena made?

102091.drop_descrip: There's room for two on this pumpkin. C'mon, hurry and get on... Ah, that reminds me! I've got some pumpkin pie as well. Wanna try some, Commander?
102091.touch2: Well made, don't you think? Heh, I've heard this thing can even harvest souls.

307072.detail: I wanted to borrow an Empyreal dress from Master Yat Sen, but it turns out we're not the same size~ So what could I do? I made it myself♡
307072.touch: Did you enjoy my performance...? Oh, my Commander~ My efforts, seeking out Master Yat Sen, the study, the practice, all that hard work... it was truly worth it~!
307072.login: My Commander, do tell me what song I might serenade you with?
307072.main: For you, my Commander, I could face any challenge...! Oh, but that little gremlin from the Eagle Union... something must be done...|If I can only keep my Commander's gaze fixed on me for just a little bit longer, all my efforts will have paid off~|If only I could become like the women in those stories... those Empyreal romances Master Yat Sen spoke of~
307072.unlock: Hehehe, I let Christmas and New Year's slip right by me, that I might use the Dragon Empery's Lunar New Year to capture my Commander's attentions... Oh, My Commander, won't you please enjoy the show I've prepared for you♡
307072.drop_descrip: Hehehe, I let Christmas and New Year's slip right by me, that I might use the Dragon Empery's Lunar New Year to capture my Commander's attentions... Oh, My Commander, won't you please enjoy the show I've prepared for you❤
307072.home: I offer you a song of joy ♡ my Commander ♪

101160.detail: Stop touching my ears! I told you already, they're real! I-I'll bite you!
101160.touch: Whoa! I actually fell asleep! Could this be because of that fabled super hypnosis thing?!
101160.login: Let's hear your excuse for making the strongest and cutest cutie in the world wait for so long, Commander!
101160.battle: It won't be as simple as going back to the title screen if we get a game over~
101160.feeling2: Ahah! What's that tasty-looking snack you've got there?
101160.mission_complete: Come on, come on! Give me a reward!
101160.main: I'm so cute! The cutest in the universe!|I'm telling you, Commander, Fletcher's house next door is full of people! Us girls need to help her out every now and then~.|If you don't talk to me enough then I'll stop being a bunny! Woof woof!
101160.feeling5: Commander! Cutie Benson has come again! I've been stopping by too often lately? That's because you haven't been paying this super duper cutie Benson a visit, so you left me no choice~ I'm not lonely at all, I swear!
101160.upgrade: My cuteness level has gone up even higher!
101160.unlock: Yahoo! Commander! Aren't you charmed by how cute and risqué I am? Huh? W-who am I? ... Hahaha... My name is Benson... It's a pleasure to meet you...
101160.feeling4: Commander, you keep telling me I'm stupid, but you actually like me, don't you?
101160.feeling1: Oh evil being who conspires against cuties... in the name of the moon, I will punish you!
101160.propose: Hehe, so you've finally noticed how important I am? Have you? Do you understand that I'm irreplaceable and that just a glance of me makes your heart skip a beat? ... Commander, why are you touching my forehead?
101160.drop_descrip: Benson-class Destroyer - Benson, Hull Number DD-421!
101160.profile: Here comes Benson! I'm way cooler than Anderson. I'm a capital destroyer, and can move at speeds up to 35 knots! My anti-air defenses are just as impressive. I can't wait for you to see me in battle!
101160.touch2: Ah, I feel so hot... I'm burning inside!
101160.mission: A mission? No problem! Easy peasy! Bring it on, whatever it may be!
101160.home: Were you thinking about how badly you wanted to come back and meet me~? Come here, I'll give a positively explosive hug! ... Hm? Fine... I'm sorry, I'll put away the dynamite... J-just hold on a minute~
101160.win_mvp: Hoho! Even the most cunning fox couldn't best a rabbit like me!
101160.expedition: Commander, the commission's been completed! I'm going to have to punish you if you forget about those girls!
101160.mail: Mail for you, Commander! I didn't want to anyone else to peek, so I went ahead and took a look myself first!
101160.feeling3: I am cuteness, and cuteness is me. Don't you agree, Commander? Yay!
101160.lose: Oh nooo! You didn't see anything, Commander! Got it?! *Sob*... I failed...

605060.detail: At last I can have a rematch with Warspite on equal terms. I've been waiting for this!
605060.touch: Mh... Mm? Sorry, I zoned out for a bit... Were you worried about me, Commander?
605060.login: You're right on time... Naturally. I'll admit your timeliness is the one thing I could learn from.
605060.battle: As per the Commander's orders, we depart for the front!
605060.hp_warning: You won't break my spirit so easily!
605060.feeling2: Cavour always stresses the importance of courtesy and diplomatic discourse, but I believe in simply speaking one's mind. Doesn't it sound dreadful to obsess over some idea of formality?
605060.mission_complete: On the topic of completing missions, does it even affect the war situation?
605060.main: Office work? Cavour is better at it than me... but I'll still do it. As any secretary should.|Commander, be decisive. Hesitation wastes time, and wasted time is gone forever.|A good leader doesn't micromanage or mediate, they issue clear orders and make firm decisions. Isn't that right, Commander?|Cavour, don't be so overly formal around the Commander! No one wants to be treated like an old-timer!
605060.feeling5: You can rest easy, Commander. For as long as I have your back, you can keep your eyes on the path ahead and continue moving forward. I'll take care of everything else for you!
605060.upgrade: I've yet to hit my own limits!
605060.unlock: I'm Giulio Cesare, battleship of the Sardegna Empire. Prove to me your talent in commanding a fleet!
605060.feeling4: A little bird told me you're free, and I've got two tickets to the opera, so what do you say? I'd say you're due for something you haven't experienced before.
605060.feeling1: Seems you lack the mindset to be a worthy commander.
605060.propose: *Sigh*... The romantic vacation I booked was all for nothing... "With who"? With you, shouldn't that be obvious?! ... "Just ask me next time"? But I booked it just for you in the first place... F-fine, I will...
605060.drop_descrip: Conte di Cavour-class battleship – Giulio Cesare.
605060.skill: All shall bow before my might!
605060.profile: Memories that haunt me? None but that dreaded battle. I had to retreat from the Battle of Punto Stilo after taking a single hit... Things would've gone differently, had I only gotten to strike first...!
605060.touch2: If you plan on toying around with me, don't blame me when you get burned.
605060.mission: You can honestly skip missions you'd rather not take on.
605060.home: Triumphant once again, yes? It's written all over your face.
605060.expedition: Isn't that the commission team? Why not go say hello to them, Commander?
couple_encourage: Our battle isn't over yet!
Cavour, worry about yourself instead!
605060.mail: There's a letter for you. Assuming it's no private matter, you don't mind if I open it, do you?
605060.feeling3: A little bit of harsh discipline is the right medicine for slouches who can't obey orders. "It's not that simple"? Well, I thought I was making a good suggestion...
605060.lose: Am I out of my depth...?!

304033.detail: I knew this kimono looked good, but your approval is what really sealed the deal, Commander. It might not be the best kimono ever, but I'll gladly take a better-than-passing grade from you!
304033.touch: Watch this, I've got a stylish move for you!
304033.login: Commander, you should get to work before Kongou gets mad at you.
304033.mission_complete: This isn't so easy to move in, but bringing the rewards here was easy as pie.
304033.main: Getting dressed was easier than you might think, because I practiced it! See, you start from the bottom and... Oh geez!|When I say I'll do something, I'll do it right! I'll prove that even I can conduct myself elegantly, as one of Kongou's sisters!|I need to go over there, so come give me a hand, Commander... Nice, thanks. I'd rather not get my kimono soaked if I can avoid it.
304033.unlock: My dear Commander, is this dress that my sisters tailored for me to your liking? ...Okay, no, I can't do polite Hiei-speak like she can... So, anyway, h-how do I look?
304033.drop_descrip: "My dear Commander, is this dress that my sisters tailored for me to your liking?" ...Okay, no, I can't do polite Hiei-speak like she can... So, anyway, h-how do I look?
304033.mission: You'd best stay focused on completing missions, Commander.
304033.home: Hold the umbrella like this... then turn around and slightly loosen the kimono... Hmm, no, this isn't really my style... How does Hiei pull it off so– Commander?! You're back?!
304033.win_mvp: How's THAT, Kirishima?! I can battle even in a kimono!

807010.detail: An improvement in operational code and tactical variables... This sequence should be useful. I shall write this down in my notebook.
807010.touch: I am right here, Commander. Do not hesitate to give me your orders.
807010.login: Here is today's schedule, Commander. Read it at your leisure.
807010.battle: Now, as outlined in our briefing, prepare for combat!
807010.hp_warning: I have sustained damage, but it is under control...
807010.feeling2: Are you curious about this book? It is just a notepad, more or less. Rest assured, there is nothing remarkable about it. And it is certainly not something you need look at.
807010.mission_complete: A mission has been completed. That's one burden off our minds.
807010.main: If I may be so blunt, Commander, it would be very unwise of you to read my book. I am not exaggerating or joking about this.|Are you daydreaming, Commander? You may continue to fantasize if you so wish; we have enough free time in today's schedule to accommodate for it.|I shall attend to our official business and schedule management. You need only focus on the work on your desk, Commander.
807010.feeling5: Commander, all of today's clerical tasks have been completed right on schedule. This is a good opportunity to... Indeed, as you've requested, I will teach you about the so-called "sacrament of love."
807010.upgrade: Your kindness will not go unrewarded, Commander.
807010.unlock: Béarn, Iris Libre's very first aircraft carrier, reporting for duty. It is an honor to fight by your side. I eagerly await your orders, Commander.
807010.feeling4: This "grimoire" topic again? I do not appreciate your insistence on it. "A sacrament from the Iris Libre can perform all sorts of miracles"... Assuming that were even true, how would you utilize such great power, Commander?
807010.feeling1: "You are the most outstanding, exceptional commander I have ever met." – You can only hope to hear me say these words in your most outlandish dreams.
807010.propose: If there are sacraments that can emotionally move and unite people, then this so-called "marriage" must be the most powerful of its kind. Ah, this bliss, this feeling of butterflies in my stomach... Now I understand how it feels to take an oath. It's quite enjoyable, actually. Hehehe~
807010.profile: My name is Béarn, I am the Iris Libre's first aircraft carrier, converted from the unfinished 5th Normandie-class dreadnought. I lived to see the end of the strife between Iris and Vichya... A tragedy I pray will never happen again.
807010.touch2: Do you lack the knowledge of what being a decent person entails, or are you simply unable to control yourself, Commander?
807010.mission: Commander, I have received word of new mission directives from headquarters. I shall go and make some arrangements.
807010.home: You would like something sugary in preparation for your mental labor? It so happens I have a list of our stock of confectionaries. Please have a look.
807010.win_mvp: How would you say I did? Was my performance satisfactory?
807010.expedition: Transport commissions and cargo escorts are vital, of course, but let's not forget the important safety of our docks.
couple_encourage: I'd love to transport fascinating items with you.
I am profoundly honored to fight by your side.
Allow me to show you an Iris sacrament.
807010.mail: Reporting in. I have a newly arrived letter for you, Commander.
807010.feeling3: A "grimoire"? Hmm... And you say L'Opiniâtre told you this? It's certainly an amusing allegory. Now, I'm afraid I must take my leave for a while, as I have business to attend to.
807010.lose: I sincerely apologize, Commander. I take full responsibility for this defeat.

202081.detail: Maid by day, and secret agent by night? Hmm, that does fit the Royal style. Unfortunately for you, it's just your imagination.
202081.touch: Master, you don't have to come all the way up to get me. It's going to be a pain to get you back down safely.
202081.login: Master, what kinds of missions are we to carry out tonight?
202081.battle: Let's hurry up and get this over with. The night wanes.
202081.main: The slumbering city, silent and dark, inexplicably makes me feel at ease... |Master, it is not incomprehensible that you would desire some excitement in your life, but please focus on the work at hand. |Do not let your guard down for even a second, and always be ready to fight. From this point, a secret agent and a maid are quite similar. Huh? Maids don't have to fight? Master, your jests are quite rich.
202081.unlock: ... Did you find out about my undercover identity? You leave me no choice. Master, I cannot allow you to leave this room... Of course I'm jesting, it's merely a hobby.
202081.drop_descrip: ... Did you find out about my undercover identity? You leave me no choice. Master, I cannot allow you to leave this room... Of course I'm jesting, it's merely a hobby.
202081.touch2: Out of respect for your bravery, I shall reserve this special bullet just for you.
202081.mail: Master, what do you plan to exchange for this all-important piece of mail?

202080.detail: Hmm? "Cleaning" things up with a gun falls perfectly within a maid's normal line of duty, Master.
202080.touch: Pest- I mean, Master, what requests do you have? I beg your pardon, that was a slip of the tongue.
202080.login: Please mind your step, Master... Right there... is where I just mopped.
202080.battle: "Garbage" will pile up if you don't "clean" it up...
202080.hp_warning: So, you pests have a few tricks up your sleeves...
202080.feeling2: I understand, Master. You've finally awakened to the realisation that you are an oversized lump of non-combustible rubbish, and your psyche is screaming for me to grant you the sweet release of... Just kidding, please wait while I make tea for you.
202080.mission_complete: Master, do you plan to give all the mission rewards to me?
202080.main: "Master, I love you." Please believe me, I put at least 30% emotion into those words. |Master, if you wish to take a nap, please tell me ahead of time. I will make sure you don't oversleep, with this gun. |Belfast dotes on you too much, Master. At this rate, I'm afraid that you will turn into a useless lump of driftwood.
202080.feeling5: Master, are you troubled by the way I talk and act toward you? If so, you must understand that is the way I express my love, my beloved Master. Yes, it's true.
202080.upgrade: Hmm... this feels a bit of all right. Thank you, Master.
202080.unlock: Ah... I thought you were a vermin, so I fired on instinct... You're my new Master? Excuse me. I am a member of the Royal Maids, Light Cruiser Sheffield. I am yours to command.
202080.feeling4: I should learn... from Belfast's example? A maid should serve her master wholeheartedly without asking for anything in return. In contrast, that one is quite greedy... but, I am a bit envious...
202080.feeling1: I see, Master, you are remarkably similar to a pest, morphologically. The world is full of mysteries.
202080.propose: Upon the name of Virgin Mary I pledge, may the hammer of love be dropped upon those that would harm my master... Master? U-um, I wasn't doing anything in particular. You must have heard me wrong. Anyway, let's get this absolutely mortifying ceremony over with as soon as possible...
202080.skill: Do you hear that? The ringing of your death knell.
202080.profile: I am the Town-class light cruiser, Sheffield. I've basically only fought against Iron Blood, having witnessed the demise of Scharnhorst, and participated in the hunt for Bismarck and Tirpitz. However, I underwent repairs throughout the end of the Second Great War and was unable to sortie. If there's nothing else you'd like to know, I would like to head back now.
202080.touch2: I do hope you have this same kind of strong spirit on the battlefield.
202080.mission: Please entrust all "cleaning" tasks to me.
202080.home: Good work, Master. There is still some work for you to take care of. Please do your best.
202080.win_mvp: Are you satisfied with these results, Master?
202080.expedition: Master, does the sound of my gun not remind you of something? Perhaps, something like the commission fleet that you've kept waiting?
couple_encourage: Surely you're not getting rusty, are you?
Do be careful with those Swordfish of yours...
I suppose this, too, is fate.
Commander, I hope this is not some perverse hobby of yours.
Let me witness your "justice."
202080.mail: Master, I've already sorted your mail.
202080.feeling3: To facilitate ease of reading, I took the liberty of organising and re-categorising all the books on your shelf. Please check the results.
202080.lose: Master, please assign me to the rear...

306010.detail: You gonna ask if I wanna go for lunch?
306010.login: Heheh... Let's get some good work done today, Commander.
306010.battle: In the name of the wings of the sky: take off!
306010.feeling2: Junyou is... I know I'm warning you about my own little sister, but she's really dangerous...
306010.mission_complete: If we keep earning honors, one day even I can become a full-fledged carrier...!
306010.main: Ah, Izumo... I'd like to meet her one day.|I'm pretty sure mine are larger than Souryuu's...|I'm slow-witted? Hmph, believe it or not, I'm a girl with a lot on her mind.
306010.feeling5: I've sent out all my planes. Right now... there's just us two in here.
306010.upgrade: ... Seems my technique's gotten more refined.
306010.unlock: Light carrier Hiyou reporting in. Commander, I won't have you looking down on the Hiyou class just 'cause we're light carriers!
306010.feeling4: My opinion of you has improved a little bit. Just a little bit, you hear!
306010.feeling1: So filthy... What? I'm not talking about you...
306010.propose: You've been real good to me, Commander... So, how about I be your lifelong partner from this day onwards...?
306010.drop_descrip: Hiyou-class aircraft carrier number one – Hiyou.
306010.profile: I'm Hiyou, Hiyou-class aircraft carrier number one. I'm a light carrier, but my damage control and loading capacity are just as good as a regular carrier's. After Midway, I was a key part of the Mobile Fleet and fought hard to my very last battle...
306010.touch2: D-didn't I tell you I was lightly armored?!
306010.mission: A mission? As long as it ain't in the Marianas, I'll take it on...
306010.home: Planes, up on deck... It's time we all get ready.
306010.win_mvp: It was all thanks to my little planes.
306010.expedition: I was actually designed with these types of missions in mind...
306010.mail: Doesn't matter if it's a pigeon or a plane delivering your mail, does it?
306010.feeling3: My eyepatch? Kinda just started wearing it on a whim. Plenty of people out there who dress like pirates, you know?
306010.lose: It's pretty hard to ignore the damage done to my planes...

202071.detail: Dressing up all Sakura style has me feeling like I want to listen to some Sakura music. Ehehe.
202071.touch: Commander, come do the shrine business with me! Let's see, I think the Sakura girls did it something like this... you put your hands together, don't you?
202071.login: Commander, Happy New Year! Now it's off to the shrine for a special blessing, isn't it? Heheh, easy does it then.
202071.main: I think this here is the "Demon Breaker Arrow," isn't it? Seems to be some kind of warding charm... brilliant!|I got one of those omikuji fortunes for you at the shrine, Commander. Let's see, what does it say...?|I find myself wanting to dive into all the girls' festivals now~ What delightful holiday do we have next? I'm so excited!
202071.unlock: Hello there~! Royal Knight Southampton is reporting for duty in a Sakura-style outfit! Hehe, don't you have something to tell me about my new look, like how cute it is? Come on, don't be shy. Speak up~
202071.drop_descrip: Hello there~! Royal Knight Southampton is reporting for duty in a Sakura-style outfit! Hehe, don't you have something to tell me about my new look, like how cute it is? Come on, don't be shy. Speak up~
202071.home: What do you say we do a bit of New Year's rearranging in the office here, make it a little easier to faff abo... Ahem, easier to polish off those official duties. Hehe.

900185.detail: Commander, what do you do for your own training? Why don't you come join us down here every now and then?
900185.touch: How strange, Commander, you're also a fan of the "bro fist?" I thought we were the only ones who used that greeting.
900185.login: Welcome back, Commander! Today's a fine day to sortie!
900185.battle: All the stars in the sky are our enemies! Everyone, fiiiiire!
900185.hp_warning: Scars are the only battle honors I need!
900185.feeling2: Before I met you, Commander, I felt like I was always trapped within Cleveland's shadow.
900185.mission_complete: We were able to complete our mission without a hitch because of everyone's superb teamwork!
900185.main: I want to fight alongside my sisters again, just like at Augusta Bay. |I want to be able to dominate the battlefield with swagger, just like Cleveland. |Even though many of my younger sisters were converted into light aircraft carriers, I'm not jealous of them at all. After all, it's best to be yourself.
900185.feeling5: Commander, you are the one who I admire and look up to the most... so if one day, you ever decide to turn your back on the person you are now, I will make sure... to drag you back!
900185.upgrade: I'll make sure to put this power to good use!
900185.unlock: Hello! I'm Denver, 4th Cleveland-class cruiser and Knight of the sea! Before I officially start working for you, I've got one question: what is the future you want to see?
900185.feeling4: Even though I don't think I can ever truly grasp the kind of future that you are envisioning, if it is something that you can stand by firmly, it must be very dazzling and beautiful.
900185.propose: Commander, your ideals and morals are loftier and purer than anyone else's... From now on, can I have the privilege of being your sword so that I may cut aside everything barring you from your future?
900185.profile: I am Denver, fourth ship of the Cleveland-class light cruisers. I fought hard alongside my sisters in the Battle of Empress Augusta Bay. Though I still lack experience, I won't let you down, Commander!
900185.touch2: Commander, what are you trying to feel for?
900185.mission: Rain or shine, hell or high water, I'm always ready to sortie!
900185.home: Welcome back! I prepared some refreshments, but... Sorry, this isn't exactly my forte.
900185.win_mvp: Let's seize the day! And the next!
900185.expedition: Let's load up some extra supplies. In a battle of attrition, we can't let supplies run out before our spirits do.
couple_encourage: Cleve, you're always kickin' ass!
900185.feeling3: I've relentlessly honed my skills in order to defeat all our enemies, but... is that really all there is to life?

202041.detail: Master, what do you think of my dress....? Oh, it looks good? Does that perhaps mean I am unworthy of it? And you want to cast me out...?! But... Masterrrrrrr...
202041.touch: Wha...?! You want to help me get ready? B-b-but to do something so mundane... And, and to do it for me... Aahh...
202041.login: Master, am I wasting your precious time...? Please forgive me! I am almost ready!
202041.main: Master, might I accompany you to the party this evening...? I swear I won't be a bother! I only ask that you occasionally acknowledge me...|Rest assured, no matter how I dress, I am ever your most loyal maid! You may ask anything of me and I will do my utmost!|Serving as your bodyguard is also one of my duties, Master! Indeed, I am here to guard you with my very life!
202041.feeling5: The party is about to begin and here you are, Master, standing by my side waiting for me... That can only mean you don't want to toss me away. That you care about me... Ooh... If only we could stay like this forever...
202041.unlock: It is so audacious for a lowly maid to dress herself in such finery and stand at her master's side... Still, I will go to my master and... M-M-Master...?!
202041.drop_descrip: It is so audacious for a lowly maid to dress herself in such finery and stand at her master's side... Still, I will go to my master and... M-M-Master...?!
202041.touch2: Master, m-my clothes are a mess... We, now... We can't...
202041.home: I cannot believe you are here and I am still getting dressed. What a worthless maid I am. Forgive me...!

304032.drop_descrip: I guess that looks right... Since Kongou chose this for me, I must trust her judgment... Um, C-Commander, would you mind helping me out? ...It's a bit hard to walk in this outfit...

202040.detail: Master, you won't abandon me, will you? Can you promise not to? Can I place my faith in you, Master? You are trustworthy, are you not? Ahh... I hope it wasn't a mistake to place my faith in you...
202040.touch: I did a good job, did I? Masterrrrr... Ah! It was nothing! J-j-j-just doing my job!
202040.login: Welcome home, Master. I am doing well, of course! Oh... m-my master is worried about me...
202040.battle: Hard work is how I'll be of use to Master! Here I come!
202040.hp_warning: I won't give up so easily...!
202040.feeling2: As a Royal Maid, I will serve my master with duty and conviction. Should you need anything of me, do not hesitate to ask.
202040.mission_complete: Congratulations, Master. The rewards from that mission look spectacular.
202040.main: Master never abandoned anyone else before, correct? Or have you just not done so *yet*? In other words, Master cares more about them than me? Blast it... I can do better than that!|Have you any work for me to do? Please, it can be anything, no matter how unimportant. Yes, that is my purpose in life, as Master's loyal maid.|It is a pleasure to see you, beloved Master. Please allow me to serve and soothe you with all my mind and body. After all, I am your personal maid, and that is my duty.
202040.feeling5: Wh-what was that? How could you possibly love a lowly maid like me...? R-really? Truly? Honestly...? The Master likes me. The Master really likes me... Ahhh.. Help, I can't stop smiling...
202040.upgrade: I cannot thank you enough, Master! But thank you very much...!
202040.unlock: Good day, Master. I am the light cruiser Dido. I am in your service as a Royal Maid.
202040.feeling4: And so it's because I'm so competent that no one worries about me... B-but you worry about me, Master? I'm unworthy of such attentions from you! I just... When I think of you, I... Aaahhh...
202040.feeling1: Ahh... I beg you, Master, spare this pitiable maid your mistreatment...
202040.propose: My... to think you could fall in love with a worthless maid... Master, I implore you! Love me forever... forever and ever and never let go...!
202040.skill: For the glory of the master!
202040.profile: I am Dido, name ship of the Dido-class. I served as an anti-aircraft cruiser in the Mediterranean during the war. By the way, I hope Sirius hasn't given you too much trouble...?
202040.touch2: M-Master... I am honored to receive your affections, but... this is most unorthodox...
202040.mission: Thank goodness... For as long as there are unfinished missions, I have a purpose.
202040.home: Master, are you all right...? Phew, glad to hear it.
202040.expedition: Master, the rewards from the commission are here. Have a look, won't you?
couple_encourage: The battlefield is the only place I need not worry about you...
202040.mail: I have mail for you, Master. Do look it over soon.
202040.feeling3: There are many klutzes among the Royal Maids, yet Master looks after them and treats them with care... I, meanwhile, am just... Oh, I'm terribly sorry! No honourable maid should be openly jealous of her companions! But still... those klutzes are such cowards...
202040.lose: I beg your forgiveness, Master! Please do not discard me like this broken doll...!

202031.detail: You are not to stray from my side at the party. Don't tell me you forgot the rules?
202031.touch: You want to see me drink? Ahaha! What an odd fetish... Here, have a goood look♪
202031.login: Commander, you're late. Don't you know the party already started?
202031.hp_warning: You soiled my dress. How bold...
202031.mission_complete: Reward...? Aha, well... How about a dance?

201104.drop_descrip: G-Good day, Master... C-Commander, please don't stare at me so much... Uuu... Saratoga told me that this was part of marketin' yourself as an idol...

202170.lose: It's not pain I fear... it's being completely helpless... Ugh!
