307080.mission_complete: As long as you are here, there is nothing that cannot be accomplished...
307080.main: Even the most beautiful flower is transient, to be scattered into the wind... But, 'tis better to bloom for but a moment than to wither eternally upon the vine.|Do you wish to rest within this one's bosom? ...Yes, just as the little destroyers do...|I would like to experience all this port has to offer... should it be possible...|I have left the report here... Hmm... There are many errors? ...'twould seem that hasty deadlines are not this one's strong suit...|Vrooom... Zzzzzz... Oh... Did I hit you by mistake? ...Sincerest apologies...
307080.feeling5: I once lamented my inability to shift the hand of fate... But now, and forever... as long as you are here...
307080.upgrade: May this not end in futility...
307080.unlock: This sensation... is that of reality... Was it you who awoke this one from her long slumber? Such is the inevitability of fate... Please allow Shinano, third ship of the Yamato-class, to guide you forward upon the right path.
307080.feeling4: Long has this one dreamt... Tragic dreams that one wishes to never recall... Blissful dreams from which one hopes to never wake from... Even reality itself seems like just another dream.. Commander, is this truly reality, or yet another illusion?
307080.feeling1: From here, this one sees not any light...
307080.propose: The memories forged at this port... have brought me great joy... Alas, from now on... I shall cherish my time with you through fates both joyful and painful... through weal and woe alike...
307080.profile: I am called Shinano, aircraft carrier of the Sakura Empire. I was to stand beside Yamato during that war, yet in the end... Alas, there is impermanence in all things, and nothing became of this one's life... May your guidance lead my fate to a different outcome...
307080.mission: This task... can it be completed in time...?
307080.home: Nnnh... Your safe return... pleases me...
307080.expedition: Mmmm... The girls on commission are returning now... 'twould behoove you to forget them not...
307080.mail: Dismiss not the letters bearing distant thoughts...
307080.feeling3: To see destiny, yet to be unable to change it; or to be ignorant to the turning of fate... Which is the greater misfortune?
307080.lose: Apologies... I have failed to meet your expectations...

101175.detail: Commander, being able to have a picnic with you and the others makes Laffey very happy... Seeing everyone getting along well also makes Laffey very happy...
101175.touch: Commander, no grabbing food with your hands...
101175.login: Commander, what's your favorite snack? Laffey is fine with anything...
101175.headtouch: Commander, do you like Laffey's bunny ears?
101175.main: We packed too many lunchboxes... Commander, help us finish them. |The bunny from the Northern Parliament gave this drink to me. She said it's best enjoyed loudly. *hic* |The sun's nice and warm... and it's making me sleepy... Commander, let's take a nap together... |Yuudachi has been going around eating all the meat... Ayanami, watch out... |Commander, poke poke... Food coma...?
101175.unlock: Commander, ahhn... Umm, Commander, Laffey does not need to be fed... Rather, Laffey should be the one feeding you...
101175.drop_descrip: Commander, ahhn... Umm, Commander, Laffey does not need to be fed... Rather, Laffey should be the one feeding you...

103140.detail: ♪ Bat outta hell~ Gets another roll~ Mess with San Fran~ Get a hole in your skull~ ♪
103140.touch: Sup? Something goin' on? Or is that your way of saying "let's hang out"? ...You wouldn't deadass poke a girl for no reason, would ya?
103140.login: ello, Puddin'! Gimme a smile! Now a high five! I see you're kicking ass at work today, so... hasta la vista baybay~!
103140.feeling2: Puddin' is a hella cute name, don'tcha think? Feels way more legit than just callin' you "commander" like everyone else.
103140.headtouch: What, you trying to spook me? Really, huh? Then you better watch for surprises from now on when you're out walkin' at night, Puddin'~
103140.mission_complete: Rewards, eh? They're all yours, Puddin'! Rewards are a crutch, I don't need 'em!
103140.main: Someone been bullyin' you, Juneau? Just tell me who, and me and my bat will go teach 'em a hard lesson!|Man, the dorm's exterior is hella drab. I could fix it up with a splash of paint, y'know.|You busy, Puddin'? Busyyyy? Helloooo? Damn, guess you're hella in the zone. Don't you get bored sittin' in here all day?|Why do I call you Puddin'? 'Cause it's fun, so why not? Haha~
103140.feeling5: Good goin' today~ Let's grab something to eat and hang out! Ahahah, c'mon, don't be scared! Grab my hand and let's go!
103140.unlock: Sup, Commander! The name's San Francisco! ...Huh, joining the fleet's supposed to be fun? Anything in it for me? Just askin' for curiosity's sake~ Oh, by the way, I'm calling ya Puddin' from now on~
103140.feeling4: Right, time to have a taste of this little puddin'~ Mm-mmh, where should I start with you? So many options! ...What? I'm just talkin' about this serving of strawberry puddin'. Get your mind outta the gutter! Hahaha~
103140.feeling1: Maybe you'll regret your jackassery if I tie you up and throw ya into the sea, eh, Puddin'?
103140.propose: Ugh, I hate ceremonies... I'll do what you say just this once. But after that, you'll be takin' orders from me, got it? Also, FYI, when I get the Puddin' munchies, it'll take a lot to calm my hunger~
103140.drop_descrip: New Orleans-class heavy cruiser – San Francisco, Hull Number CA-38.
103140.profile: I'm San Francisco, the legendary New Orleans-class heavy cruiser! I made it through the war alive by clobberin' suckers left and right! Now I just wanna do my own thing, chilling, kickin' it, that kind of stuff!
103140.touch2: All right then, let's clobber some decency into you! ...Just messin', but don't do that again, 'kay?
103140.mission: This mission? Looks like a cakewalk to me. It's all yours, Puddin'.
103140.home: A wild Puddin' appeared! Now let's see if you're gonna work hard or hardly work!
103140.win_mvp: Dusted and done! Those chumps never stood a chance, Puddin'.
103140.expedition: Welcome the commission team back? Naw, that's outta my pay grade. Now, if I get to meet some chill people, then we're talkin'!
couple_encourage: No friendly fire this time, I promise!
Bring me the next time you go hunting!
Let's do this, fluffball!
If you need a gaming buddy, I'm your gal!
Eagle Union, roll out!
103140.mail: Seems you've got new mail. I'm hella beat right now, so fetch it yourself.
103140.feeling3: Oh boy, what to do today~? Maybe I'll get up to some fun hijinks before Puddin' catches on to what I'm doing~
103140.lose: Don't get bummed out~ I'll win twice as hard for you next time!

304041.detail: Commander, how about we go flower-viewing later after school?
304041.login: Commander, your necktie is crooked. Want me to straighten it out for you?
304041.main: nil|Commander, if there's anything troubling you, you can always tell me.|I haven't picked a club to join yet... The Archery Club? That actually sounds pretty good... Huh? I'm "not suited for that"?
304041.unlock: Commander, enjoying school life is all fine and well, but we must not forget our duty... That said, what missions are waiting for us today?
304041.drop_descrip: Commander, enjoying school life is all fine and well, but we must not forget our duty... That said, what missions are waiting for us today?
304041.home: I made some sweets for my classmates. Let's hand them out together later.
304041.mail: "Mailing" seems to have gotten pretty popular at school lately. Thanks to that, I've gotten pretty good at writing.

203040.detail: My post-retrofit performance is very impressive!
203040.login: Commander, you're back! Me? I'm looking at the clouds.
203040.feeling2: Hmm, clear skies, so a great day to scout out the waters~ Do you want to come with me, Commander?
203040.mission_complete: Commander! How can you also be so forgetful and forget to collect your rewards?
203040.main: My greatest accomplishments were done just watching the waves like this.|Commander, want to watch the clouds with me? I bet we'll see some wonderful things!|Don't look at me like that, I've been to plenty of places before!
203040.feeling5: Even though it's nice to receive compliments, I am much happier just being able to support you the best I can, Commander.... Why is that?
203040.upgrade: Now I can protect myself even if I get lost again!
203040.unlock: Where am I...? Ah, excuse me! Do you kno....Oh! You're the commander? This is great! I'm Suffolk, I finally found you!
203040.feeling4: My big sisters are so strong, if only I could be of more help to them... Huh? I'm doing a good job as well? Hehehe... I received a compliment~
203040.propose: Hmph, the Commander has finally noticed that under all that hazziness there is brilliance to be found! From now on I can be as lazy as I want. ... Huh? I can't?
203040.drop_descrip: Kent-class heavy cruiser - Suffolk, Hull Number 55!
203040.profile: I'm the fifth ship of the Kent-class. Although I look like this, I can still pull it off when it counts. During the Battle of the Denmark Strait, I basically saved the day!
203040.touch2: ... Ah! Commander! If you were here you should have said something.
203040.mission: The weather sure is nice... Oh? Commander! You've got some new missions.
203040.home: Good work, Commander! Care for a cup of tea?
203040.win_mvp: That cloud looks like a.... Oh? We won?
203040.expedition: That cloud looks like cotton candy... hmm? Ah, Commander. The commission team is back~!
203040.mail: Commander... hm... what did I want to say... Ah, right! New mail for you!
203040.feeling3: Reconnaissance is a very important task! Huh, I'm losing focus? W-what are you saying? I'm just o-observing the weather...
203040.lose: *Cries*... If only I had paid more attention...

108071.detail: Bunny suits are made to imitate bunnies. If you like bunny girls, that means you also like bunnies, right? Um, it doesn't work like that?
108071.touch: Huh? My earrings are on crooked?
108071.login: Commander, I'm over here. (*whispers*) I, I was noticed, right...
108071.main: Commander, your coffee's already gone cold. Huh, I forgot to remind you earlier....?|The Almanac of Marine Life was really interesting. I really want to see all those mysterious creatures in person.|I'm really good at hide-and-seek. When I was playing with Dace, I managed to stay hidden 'til the very end! Teehee~
108071.unlock: Phew~ Standing for a long time really wears you out... Hwah?! Commander, when'd you get there? Um, if you'd like, would you like to come exercise with me?
108071.drop_descrip: Phew~ Standing for a long time really wears you out... Hwah?! Commander, when'd you get there? Um, if you'd like, would you like to come exercise with me?
108071.home: Um, Commander, I'm not standing behind the door, so you don't have to be that careful.

207028.touch: Interested in trying my home cooking? I've trained under the Royal Maids, and I'm 99% sure I can prepare a good meal!
207028.main: nil|nil|nil|I brandish my rigging to protect this sacred moment in time!
207028.feeling5: Since we've grown so intimate, I assume it's now safe to tell you that I've become... r-r-rather intimate with the little destroyers too! Of course, you are still number one in my heart, Your Excellency!
207028.unlock: I never thought a day would come when even I don such attire... Ahem. Your Excellency, I shall protect your happiness, as well as that of my destroyer sisters!
207028.drop_descrip: I never thought a day would come when even I don such attire... Ahem. Your Excellency, I shall protect your happiness, as well as that of my destroyer sisters!
207028.home: Taking a leisure break, I assume? Then won't you accompany me to check on the little destroyers, Your Excellency?
207028.mail: Allow me to read your letter aloud, Your Excellency.

108070.detail: Submarines were born in an attempt to imitate the nautilus. When you look at things that way, the ideas for a lot of inventions were derived from animals.
108070.login: Good morning, Commander. I popped out of nowhere again? Actually, I've been behind you this whole time.
108070.feeling2: Ugh... I'm so sorry, Commander. I didn't do it on purpose... I was just trying to follow you for a little longer...
108070.headtouch: Nautilus is not a small animal...
108070.mission_complete: We're all done with the mission... Huh? I was a great help to you?
108070.main: I wish I could dive deeper and get to know the secrets of the sea...|Commander, want to try writing a message-in-a-bottle? Someone across the ocean might read it one day.|Commander? Oh, um, it's nothing. I was just wondering if you noticed me or not...
108070.feeling5: Commander, you're taking a different route than normal today... Oh, um, you wanted to go somewhere a bit more private for the two of us? I, I see! O-of course I'd be glad to accompany you! Hehe~
108070.upgrade: I hope... my torpedo doesn't end up being a dud again...
108070.unlock: Nice to meet you, Commander. I'm Nautilus from the Eagle Union... Um, did I scare you? A-actually, I've been following you this whole time, so I thought you already noticed me...
108070.feeling4: Commander, are you, um, going on a walk right now? You always go around this time to catch a breather. I know this from experience, hehe.
108070.feeling1: Commander, you're going to become even more of a loner at this rate...
108070.propose: Ehehe, Commander, if you like me that much... O-of course I'd be glad to remain with you forever~♪
108070.profile: I'm Nautilus, Narwhal-class submarine – Ah, um, not that "Captain Nemo." During that war, my friends shot at me by mistake, and I managed to do something incredible without realizing it... Overall, I think ended up being quite useful to everyone...
108070.mission: Commander, you seem to have quite a few missions still. I'd like to be of use to you in some way...
108070.home: Hauu! ...Commander, it's not your fault, so please don't apologize. I wasn't standing behind the door on purpose...
108070.win_mvp: Huh? I'm the MVP? How'd that happen?
108070.expedition: Hehe, I took a little sneak peek, and there's a lot of goodies.
108070.mail: Commander, did you get the new mail? Phew, thank goodness...
108070.feeling3: Umm, I'm not a stalker. I'm not trying to make a hobby out of sneaking up on people either... It's just that, I like being with you, Commander... so I end up following you around... Ehehe.
108070.lose: What should I do if everyone mistakes me for an enemy...?

202171.detail: Boss, if you have time, wanna help me upgrade my bike? I got some sick ideas.
202171.touch: Boss, do you wanna try riding too? Be careful, this guy's got some serious horsepower.
202171.login: Boss, the weather be fine today. Wanna go for a ride?
202171.main: When somethin' is on my mind, I just keep on riding until my troubles are left far, far behind... However, it's really easy to get lost. |Boss, when I drive, I like to go fast. When you're sitting behind me, make sure to hold on tight! |Boss, what if I named this bad boy here "Dark Bolt?"
202171.feeling5: I used to consider myself a drifter, a vagabond with no home and no destination. But I learned that I was wrong, Boss. No matter what happens, I'll always come back... to home.
202171.unlock: Hey Boss, you talkin' about my sweet bike? Heh, I made it myself by scrounging up parts from Akashi's place. Pretty cool, huh?
202171.drop_descrip: Hey Boss, you talkin' about my sweet bike? Heh, I made it myself by scrounging up parts from Akashi's place. Pretty cool, huh?
202171.touch2: Boss... even though I told you to hold on to me tight, I didn't mean right there...
202171.home: Boss, come take a seat. We're gonna forget all about the the smoke of the battlefield, and feel the wind at our side.

108041.detail: I've heard I can throw the ball faster if I have my feet raised, like a pitcher! ...It doesn't work like that?
108041.touch: Is... this the proper throwing stance? I'll memorize it!
108041.login: I wish baseball was as easy as diving... I'll still give it my best shot, though! Bluegill's a go-getter!
108041.main: With you and Coach Bogue helping me, I'm destined to become a pro player!|I'll stun everyone with my skills when the next baseball league rolls around!|Intrepid! Bluegill's by your back! Don't forget that!
108041.unlock: Look out for Bluegill's ultra-reliable defense, Intrepid! Hehehe, Commander, stay here and see the results of Bluegill's special training!
108041.drop_descrip: Look out for Bluegill's ultra-reliable defense, Intrepid! Hehehe, Commander, stay here and see the results of Bluegill's special training!
108041.home: Bluegill catches, Bluegill throws! Oh no! Look out! Sorry, Commander, I didn't mean to throw it at you! Hehehe...

108032.detail: Here, Commander! A bouquet for you! I heard from Shoukaku that you like these!
108032.touch: A toast to the party! Hehehe~ That's how you do it, right?
108032.login: Oh! I've been waiting for you, Commander! I was seriously worried that you'd gotten yourself lost!
108032.main: I'll gather up tons of balloons then take off into the sky! Yeah, as if! Hehehe~|Hrrmm, still not old enough to drink, huh... I'm not a kid anymore, so what's the big deal?!|Teach me how to dance, Commander! I wanna do it with you like everyone else does!
108032.unlock: Look at all the cute balloons and flowers, and the delicious food as well! Hehe! Parties are the best!
108032.drop_descrip: Look at all the cute balloons and flowers, and the delicious food as well! Hehe! Parties are the best!
108032.touch2: I'm gonna tell on you for that!
108032.home: Hey Gridley, come take a pic of me and the Commander! Thanksies!

304040.detail: Kongou brought me some tea. How about we drink it together?
304040.touch: Were you starting to feel lonely, Commander?
304040.login: Commander, is there anything I can help with?
304040.battle: My cannons will decide this battle!
304040.hp_warning: This is it... The beginning of the end!
304040.feeling2: Hiei manages to always stay calm, no matter the situation...
304040.mission_complete: Those girls seem exhausted from their commission. Let's go and carry them back to the dormitory.
304040.main: Searchlights? Ahahahah... The battlefield is no stage.|Why I wear this mask? Hahah, think you can guess why?|Kongou, allow me to help... What? Y-you don't want any help, huh...
304040.feeling5: There'll be a dance at a party Hiei is organizing, so... could you be my dance partner? I mulled over it a bit, but you're really my only choice... Huh? Normally, it's the man who asks his partner for a dance? Ahahah, right, how stupid of me...
304040.upgrade: I wonder what'll become of me if these improvements continue...
304040.unlock: I'm Kirishima, the fast battleship! Now, Commander, there's a long road ahead of us, and we should walk down it together!
304040.feeling4: You know, my big sisters are both really brilliant. That's why I have to work so hard not to hold them back... You think I'm brilliant, too? Hahahah, I'm happy to receive your approval.
304040.feeling1: Well, guess even you have problems you won't tell others about...
304040.propose: I-I never would've expected an attack from you... Well, this is embarrassing... *A-ahem*! Then, to return the favor... Commander, whenever you need a dance partner, I'll be yours.
304040.drop_descrip: Kongou-class fast battleship number four – Kirishima.
304040.profile: I am Kirishima, the youngest of the Kongou-class fast battleships. I once bombarded Henderson Field and that battleship South Dakota. Searchlights... and Type 3 Shells? ... Aha, hahaha...
304040.touch2: I'm right here, Commander. Face your partner square on if you're going to do that. Ahahah, look at you~ Now it's you who's embarrassed.
304040.mission: Hum, hum. What should I take home with me as a souvenir...
304040.home: You're doing good work out there, Commander. For the next battle, what do you say about bringing me along?
304040.win_mvp: When I use all my power, this is only natural.
304040.expedition: You're knee-deep in paperwork... Want some help?
couple_encourage: Prove to me that you're worthy of being known as the Strongest Shield!
Kongou, you're looking elegant as ever.
Hiei, try stay close to me this time!
Haruna, why don't we settle things with a match?
304040.mail: You have mail. You must be really popular, Commander.
304040.feeling3: Haruna and I are twins, but to me she feels more like an annoying little sister.
304040.lose: Being able to meet one's demise in a battle of firepower might not be so unfortunate...

301620.detail: Midway? I believe we won that battle... O-or am I wrong again?!
301620.touch: Wah! I wish you'd stop poking my cheek like that... Mmph...
301620.login: I'm right here if you need me.
301620.battle: Destroyer Division 17, setting sail! Huh? Did I get something wrong...?
301620.feeling2: I still don't know very much about you, Commander.
301620.mission_complete: I knew you could do it, Commander.
301620.main: Hamakaze-chan, you need to ease up a little! Pokey-poke~|Y-Yukikaze's coming here? W-we should be able to get along... Hopefully...|I always feel at ease when you're here with me, Commander.
301620.feeling5: When I'm with you, it feels like time flows faster. Do you feel the same thing, Commander?
301620.unlock: I am Tanikaze, the winds have carried me from valleys to mountaintops... Commander, will you take me home?
301620.feeling4: Hehe~ You're wide open for attack! Poke~
301620.propose: Ahh... Th-thank you so much... I-I happily accept. Um... uh, well, I-I... love you too, Commander! I-I'm so embarrassed...
301620.profile: I'm Tanikaze, Kagerou-class destroyer number fourteen. I served as the flagship of Destroyer Division 17. There were a lot of aircraft in the Battle of Midway, but I hardly got bombed at all. Hamakaze-chan and I sunk a certain ship in the Kula Gulf... Hehehe~
301620.touch2: Please, don't poke anything but my cheek!
301620.mission: The mission isn't finished yet, Commander.
301620.win_mvp: Did I do well enough to satisfy you, Commander?
301620.expedition: A team has returned to base, Commander.
couple_encourage: Let's fight like we did in the Kula Gulf!
301620.mail: The winds have brought you new mail.
301620.feeling3: Usually valley winds are only there during noon, but I'm always here!
301620.lose: What could I have done better...

108030.detail: I'm no fish out of water that can't fight on the surface! It's no problem for me!
108030.touch: Ahahaha~! Stop! Ahahah~! That tickles– ahahaha!
108030.login: Morning! You're right on time today!
108030.hp_warning: I won't give up, no matter how bad it gets!
108030.feeling2: Fear of failure can be overcome by showing your courage!
108030.mission_complete: Ooh! A boatload of rewards! Let's treat ourselves, Commander!
108030.main: Could we make submarines stronger? By, for example... giving them stronger, better weapons or something?|It's so boring to just sit here and twiddle my thumbs... Give me something to do, Commander!|Whew! The breeze feels almost as good on land as it does at sea!
108030.feeling5: I had a dream where you carried me and walked around the port... It was really weird! But for some strange reason, it makes me feel happy... I wonder why...
108030.unlock: I'm Cavalla, the Eagle Union submarine! I'll make this fleet famous through glorious victories, so just you wait, Commander!
108030.feeling4: I've been feeling sick lately... I can't fight with the same flair as I used to when I think about you... That's it, it's gotta be your fault, Commander! ... Actually, I'm not so sure...
108030.propose: Whuah! Hold on a sec! Why are you hugging me out of the blue?! What are you doing?! You call this "weight training"? A-are you kidding me?! Everyone's staring at us, so let go already!
108030.drop_descrip: Gato-class submarine – Cavalla, Hull Number SS-244.
108030.skill: I've been waiting for this chance!
108030.profile: I was given a golden opportunity during my maiden voyage and sank a carrier! ... It was a pretty risky move, and it wasn't easy! But in the end, I came out on top! If you wanna hear the whole story, just ask!
108030.mission: Do we get a boatload of rewards if we do these missions?
108030.home: Commander, if you need the expertise of a submarine, just call on Cavalla!
108030.win_mvp: You can thank Cavalla for this victory! Hehehe~
108030.expedition: The commission team has returned safely!
couple_encourage: Let's see who of us is the strongest!
108030.mail: A new message has arrived! Wonder if it's from one of my submarine friends!
108030.feeling3: Sometimes, courage alone isn't enough... And that's when I need your strength, Commander! With your instructions, we can overcome anything!
108030.lose: Bah... This happened just cause the sea is so salty...

108021.detail: You wanna warn people about my firecrackers? Hehehe~ By all means, go ahead~ But how exactly are you gonna explain knowing that I had 'em hidden under my dress~? You get where I'm going with this, don'tcha? Hehehe~
108021.touch: You're gonna dig up location info under the guise of dancing with someone? Hey, pretty good idea! Huh? You just wanna dance? With me?
108021.login: How about a... KAPOW! Gave you a real scare, didn't I? Teehee~ Turned out pretty good, if I say so myself~
108021.main: Commander, you seen Taihou anywhere? I've got an explosive surprise for her!|Which do you like more: this dress, or my ordinary getup? Why do I even ask? Hehehe~ C'mon, don't be shy and answer the question~|Over here, Commander! You agreed to be my accomplice right when you caught wind of my plan, so you've gotta follow me around the whole day~
108021.feeling5: L-listen, I'm really grateful that you hang out and let me mess around with you! I've got something important to say... Come here so I can whisper... C'mon, a little closer... *smooch*♡ Hah, got 'em! Expect much more teasing to come~
108021.unlock: Oopsie! I totally just dropped something by mistake~! I'd better pick it up quick! Hmm? Saw something you shouldn't have, Commander? Hehehe~ That makes you my partner in crime now!
108021.drop_descrip: Oopsie! I totally just dropped something by mistake~! I'd better pick it up quick! Hmm? Saw something you shouldn't have, Commander? Hehehe~ That makes you my partner in crime now!
108021.touch2: I wonder how people would look at you if I set off a firecracker right now... Wanna find out? Heheheh~
108021.home: Time to spice up Cavalla's drink with a little... Darnit, you caught me in the act, Commander... All I wanted to do was give it a more mature but alcohol-free taste!

402040.detail: C-commander... Please don't stare at me...
402040.touch: Is this training for learning how to not faint? I'll.. see what I can do...
402040.login: Wel... welcome back, Commander. I've arranged your documents...
402040.battle: Ahh~! I'm so nervous I could faint...
402040.feeling2: Commander, y-you called for me? Ah... a d-d-date??! ... (faints)
402040.mission_complete: Ah- Wah! Commander, your rewards have arrived...
402040.main: Eek! I think I saw something...|I'll... I'll try my best!|Commander... is there anything else I can help with?
402040.feeling5: Fishy... you're on lookout duty... I've got something very important to tell Commander... Don't let anyone in...
402040.unlock: Co- Commander... I'm Leipzig. I black out frequently due to malnutrition, but... I'll do my best to finish the tasks assigned to me...
402040.feeling4: For the longest time, only Fishy would keep me company. Commander... for you to accept me... I'm so happy!
402040.propose: I'm so glad that you returned my feelings, Commander. I'll do my best... not to faint in front of you anymore.
402040.drop_descrip:
Leipzig-class light cruiser, Leipzig.
<color=#ffde38>Can be built after unlocking</color>
402040.profile:
Um... I'm... Leipzig, the first ship of the Leipzig-class...
One time, I collided with Eugen because of some thick fog... I hope she doesn't still hate me...
402040.touch2: Uuu... I really won't be able to move like this... what should I do?
402040.mission: Commander... you've been assigned new missions...
402040.win_mvp: I feel stronger with Commander around...
402040.expedition: Ah, Commander! Fishy told me that the girls have returned from their commission...
402040.mail: Commander, Fishy brought in some new mail...
402040.feeling3: I won't faint anymore after I've gotten used to it... Also, Commander, being with you... makes me really happy.
402040.lose: Wah... I'll be bitten... It's scary! I'm not going!

108010.detail: The gleam of the metal, the coolness to the touch, the distinctive splash, and of course, the explosion... Ahh, Commander, torpedoes are simply the best!
108010.touch: Commander, have you ever seen a dozen torpedoes go off at once? Don't you think it'd make for an awesome light show?
108010.login: Ah, Commander, good timing! Mind helping me pick up those torpedoes next to your feet~?
108010.battle: Torpedoes locked, loaded, and ready to go~!
108010.hp_warning: Um... did they find our hiding place...?
108010.feeling2: Today's a good day to shoot a bunch of torpedoes!
108010.mission_complete: Mission rewards-attached torpedoes, laaaaunch~! Commander, I'm not sure you'll be able to catch this one~!
108010.main: "Dace's Torpedo Circus." It's always been a dream of mine to make that happen one day! |Commander, I'm going to give you a crash course on torpedoes! Trust me, you'll be fascinated! |Commander, wanna have some torpedo chocolate or torpedo bread? Here, have some, I made 'em myself!
108010.feeling5: Hmm... if I had to choose between Commander and my torpedoes... Urgh, there are a lot of torpedoes out there but only one Commander, so I suppose I'll pick Commander! Mmhmm, that's right!
108010.upgrade: Commander, did you remember to prioritize upgrading the torpedoes first?
108010.unlock: Hi~ are you my new commander? I'm Dace from the Eagle Union, reporting for duty. I believe in shooting torpedoes first, and asking questions later~
108010.feeling4: Commander, won't you come see my torpedo show next time? If you're not there, I can't get hyped at all... so, promise you'll be there!
108010.feeling1: You're banned from the Torpedo Lovers Club!
108010.propose: This is for me? Really? Ehehe~ I'm so happy! Commander, it's a promise, okay? In return, I promise that if you order me to shoot a torpedo in one direction, I won't also shoot them in every other direction!
108010.profile: The name's Dace! My three favorite things are torpedoes, torpedo launchers, and uh, more torpedoes! My class? Oh right, I'm a Gato-class... If I remember properly, one of my achievements included taking out that Maya fellow... wonder if she's around.
108010.touch2: Torpedo volley! Locked on to Commander~!
108010.mission: Commander! Ah, um, do you have any missions that require some serious torpedo launching?
108010.home: Good work out there, Commander! Here's a torpedo for you! Huh, what's it for? For hugging of course - it'll help you sleep comfortably when you're tired!
108010.win_mvp: Heheh~ how do ya like them torpedoes!
108010.expedition: The commission fleet has returned! How nice, I'd love to go out and shoot some... Ah, no no, this is commissions that we're talking about! Commander? Heey~ Commander!
108010.mail: Commander! Mail's here! Check if my torpedoes are here~!
108010.feeling3: Maya really packs a punch... I suppose she just got careless that time. Well, it is the job of a submarine to catch people off guard.
108010.lose: Let... Lemme shoot off a few more at least!

107382.detail: One needs knowledge to write a story. Knowledge on ships, on people, and on the world as a whole. Say, Commander, has anyone ever told you, "Read a book or two"? Hehehe~
107382.touch: Ah, I believe a theory recently surfaced, claiming that dinosaurs were feathery, not scaly. But what do you think, Commander?
107382.main: It seems I can only make notes and sketches as there's no photography allowed here... I'm a little annoyed by that.|Wait, Intrepid! Don't run around recklessly! Good grief... Could you please go help her out, Commander?|Though not as old as these fossils, there have been relics found that indicate saffron was being cultivated during the Bronze Age. Incidentally, would you care for some tea if you're thirsty, Commander?
107382.unlock: This specimen looks to be fairly ancient... You could watch from behind me, or you could join me for an up-close examination; we can enjoy our time here however you wish.
107382.drop_descrip: This specimen looks to be fairly ancient... You could watch from behind me, or you could join me for an up-close examination; we can enjoy our time here however you wish.
107382.touch2: Should I respond like a dinosaur and go, "Graaawr!" for you? Hehehe~
107382.home: What are your thoughts on this specimen, Commander? Hehe, would you say it befits your glory?

303110.detail: Small strokes fell great oaks, constant drops pierce through rock. Those who train through the most humdrum of days shall seize victory in the most critical of moments. That is my belief.
303110.touch: E-enemies?! Oh... It was you, Commander? Apologies - my eyesight isn't the best.
303110.login: {namecode:66} standing by. What are your orders?
303110.battle: Please leave combat to me. I shall not shame my title of being "The Strongest!"
303110.feeling2: Do you need anything? If not, I'm going back to work.
303110.mission_complete: Mission accomplished! Are we going to collect the rewards?
303110.main: Even back in port, we must not lower our guard. Danger lurks around every corner.|Commander, not even you could withstand my blade.|Daily refinement means to continually strive towards your goals. Commander, may your focus never falter.
303110.feeling5: No matter how badly I'm injured, I will make sure to always return to your side. So... Commander, could you always stay with me as well?
303110.unlock: Are you the Commander? Please allow this lowly {namecode:66} to offer you what little strength she has.
303110.feeling4: Recently, I haven't been able to keep my composure during training.. Just from thinking about you, my form becomes sloppy. If I am like this, would you still want to keep me by your side?
303110.feeling1: A sword has no eyes. It would be wise to avoid approaching me casually.
303110.propose: For you to acknowledge me like this, Commander, is the greatest honor. From now on, this blade shall serve only you. Please continue to treat me kindly.
303110.drop_descrip: First ship of the {namecode:66}-class heavy cruisers, {namecode:66}.
303110.profile: I am {namecode:66}, first ship of the {namecode:66}-class heavy cruisers. I may not look like it, but I have already crossed through countless battlefields. Please place your faith in my firepower and armor, and be at ease.
303110.touch2: Kyaa! You scared me... how shameless!
303110.mission: New tasks have been assigned - would you like to confirm them?
303110.home: I'm glad that you came back safe and sound.
303110.win_mvp: Hm... Once again, I've cut a worthless object.
303110.expedition: Your fleet has returned from commission. Want to welcome them back?
303110.mail: Commander, there's new mail. Shall I bring it for you?
303110.feeling3: It might be pretty nice to just set aside my duties and have a relaxing conversation with you every once in a while, Commander.
303110.lose: I was careless... I definitely will not fail next time!

107380.detail: I strictly follow the principle of divulging nothing to outsiders, but giving full disclosure to my superior officers.
107380.touch: Which story would you like to hear, Commander? The one about the undiscovered haven, or the wonderland beyond the horizon?
107380.login: Welcome back, Commander. I recorded all the noteworthy events that took place while you were gone. Would you care to read about them?
107380.battle: Turn bow to the wind! We shall teach them the importance of freedom!
107380.hp_warning: Put out the fire! Please, hurry!
107380.feeling2: Starting today, I will take notes on everything related to you, Commander.
107380.headtouch: My hair ornaments? They're a gift from Yat Sen; she said they go well with my name.
107380.mission_complete: A mission has been completed. I wonder what our reward will be. Perhaps an unmanned recon aircraft?
107380.main: Are you curious about these butterflies? Bugwatching is one of my hobbies, actually. I brought these darlings with me from Panama.|Anti-sub warfare? I'd love to try my hand at it, should the opportunity arise. Who knows, I may be surprisingly talented!|Ensuring you stay in good health is part of my job, Commander. I sincerely urge you to be careful so as to not overwork yourself.
107380.feeling5: Did you know that the saffron flower symbolizes joy in floriography? To me, writing your biography, fighting by your side, and personally looking after you... That is the greatest joy of my life.
107380.upgrade: Thank you. I will repay your generosity with greater glory in battle.
107380.unlock: CV-38, Shangri-La, has arrived. I'd like to share the stories in this notebook with you someday... but first, let's concentrate on the task at hand.
107380.feeling4: *sigh*, I've asked you time and time again to be more health-conscious... Please, have this cup of saffron tea. It's good for you.
107380.feeling1: You've been added to my confidential informee blacklist, Commander. Do keep that in mind.
107380.propose: I'd love to write down my feelings without a moment's delay, but a more important task is at hand: holding you in a close embrace. I, Shangri-La, will forever be with you, following you to the mystical land at the end of your journey.
107380.drop_descrip: Essex-class aircraft carrier – Shangri-La, Hull Number CV-38.
107380.skill: Weather the storm and fight with all your might!
107380.profile: My name, Shangri-La, has its origins in a famous operation from the war. Being an Essex-class, I've been all over the world and got to record a myriad of things and events in my notebook. This, to me, is my source of pride.
107380.touch2: Did you just perform a health examination on me?
107380.mission: We've received a mission from headquarters. I made note of it in our task list.
107380.home: The fleet has returned to port. Let us hold a tactical debriefing once everyone has had some time to rest.
107380.win_mvp: Shangri-La will forever be out of reach to the likes of you.
107380.expedition: A commission has been completed. Shall go and we receive the returning team?
couple_encourage: Don't worry too much, I'm sure we will one day surpass Enterprise.
Would you mind lending me some aircraft, Miss... Umm, "Miss Cowgirl"?
107380.mail: You've received new mail. If you're short on time, you could consider having me read it out for you.
107380.feeling3: Commander, no matter how pressed for time you may be, eating junk food will only impact your health negatively. Please, I urge you to have this more healthy sandwich I made.

402030.detail: Commander, what kind of data are you looking for?
402030.login: Welcome back, Commander. Here is today's schedule. Please look it over.
402030.feeling2: Is there anything that I can help with? Please let me know.
402030.mission_complete: Mission complete! Shall I take an inventory of the rewards?
402030.main: Ah... We went over budget again this month...|Königsberg, stop teasing the Commander! Be careful or you might just awaken some weird fetish of his...|Karlsruhe, Commander is very busy right now. Can't you stop bothering him and just play by yourself?
402030.feeling5: J-jeez... Am I really the only one who can rein you in, Commander? Just let me handle all your affairs, private or public. Wh-what? I'm not trying to make you my property!
402030.upgrade: Commander, you're a very kind person... for taking care of your subordinates.
402030.unlock: You seem like a wise Commander. I'm Köln. Please rest assured and let me take care of your work.
402030.feeling4: To... to prevent you from harassing my sisters... I-I will... (blushes)
402030.feeling1: Workplace harassment is a crime, Commander...
402030.propose: With this... I can get much closer to Commander! A-ahem... it's nothing! Thank you, Commander, I won't let you down.
402030.profile:
I'm the third ship of the Königsberg-class light cruisers, Köln. Our slender bodies are something that we're all very proud of.
I once circumnavigated the world, and participated in operations in the Baltic Sea and North Sea. You can count on me for any type of operations, defense or assault!
402030.touch2: Commander... You realize that harrassing one's subordinates is despicable, right?
402030.mission: New missions have been posted. Shall I add them to today's schedule?
402030.home: Good work, Commander. The next thing on the agenda is...
402030.win_mvp: Phew... This performance... should be acceptable?
402030.expedition: Your fleet has returned from their commission. Should I join you for the inspection?
402030.mail: There's new mail for you, Commander. Please take a look.
402030.feeling3: I'm so glad that you are an approachable superior. I can't really handle short-tempered people.
402030.lose: Ugh... I failed again. P-please don't dismantle me...

102088.detail: Is my June bride look just the bestest or what!
102088.login: I've already finished today's work and did it all in a flash! Now c'mon, it's time to have fun!
102088.battle: San Diego, moving out! Go, go, go!
102088.main: So, Commander! You mind having tonight's dinner microwaved? Is the bath at 50 degrees all cool with you? Don't answer, 'cause San Diego went and did it all already!|Man, San Juan's such a worrywart~ I'll be just fine, 'cause I've got you, Commander! Everything's gonna be right as rain!|I'll cheerlead for you, Commander! Hip, hip, hooray! One, two, three! Whoop-de-doo!
102088.feeling5: It's kinda weird, but I get this feeling like thinking of you makes me grow stronger, Commander! Wait, doesn't that mean I'm gonna change eventually? Nope! 'Cause I'm gonna be your number one!
102088.unlock: Commander, with the power of your love, San Diego is sure to become number one in this port! ...Number one in what? I'm not really sure myself, but I'll definitely make it happen!
102088.drop_descrip: Commander, with the power of your love, San Diego is sure to become number one in this port! ...Number one in what? I'm not really sure myself, but I'll definitely make it happen!
102088.home: Welcome back, Commander! Your sweetie San Diego's been waiting for you!

10400030.detail: What type of music do you listen to, Commander? I have a great artist recommendation for you! Her name's Kizuna AI... Oh wait, that's me!
10400030.touch: Oh, are you requesting a song? Sure thing, what do you wanna hear? I'll sing it for you!
10400030.login: Welcome back! I got some singing lessons from Saratoga in preparation for my next concert. Give me your ear for a sec!
10400030.battle: Let's build some hype for this battle!
10400030.hp_warning: I'll see this through all the way to the end!
10400030.feeling2: I wanna host a concert here at the port! Could you collab with me on it, Commander?
10400030.mission_complete: Let's go get those mission rewards! Do you think we'll get anything good?
10400030.main: That was great, Z35! Oh, hi, Commander! I just got to hear Z35 practice her singing!|Check it out, this thing is so flappy! You want me to jump? Too bad for you this isn't a skirt.|Huh? You think I'm cute? Uh-huh! I already knew that, but thanks!
10400030.feeling5: We totally nailed that concert! I'm so glad you were there to help. Oh, right! I've got a special song just for you. Please lend me your ear!
10400030.upgrade: Strengthening complete! ♪ You know, concerts and battles both take a lot of strength!
10400030.unlock: Kizuna AI here, wearing a dress, coming at you! Be it concert or combat, I'll give it my all!
10400030.feeling4: Hey, Commandeeeer! What's up? Huh? You've already prepared a stage and everything?! Holy cow! I just gotta focus on practicing my skills? ... W-wow, you seem like a super capable guy, Commander!
10400030.feeling1: Relax, I'm not inviting you to my concert anyway.
10400030.propose: Moving in synch with the others, singing, dancing, and smiling! That's what a concert's about. That's the image in my mind... Thank you so much, Commander! But, of course, this doesn't mean the end! Let's go, Commander! I'm counting on you!
10400030.drop_descrip: Kizuna AI here, wearing a dress, coming at you! Be it concert or combat, I'll give it my all!
10400030.profile: This is the costume I wear for my concerts! I hope one day this port will be able to host a concert, too!
10400030.touch2: You want a high five? Let's do it! Yeeeaahhh!
10400030.mission: Alrighty, looks like we've got a new message notification. Let's get it done, right away!
10400030.home: Well done, Commander! I was just about to have a dance lesson with Cygnet and her friends. We've got time before the next sortie, so come along!
10400030.win_mvp: Per-fect vic-tory! But of course! I'm a genius!
10400030.expedition: Those commission girls are back now! We should give them a welcoming song! C'mon, sing with me, Commander!
couple_encourage: Chunechune, I'll keep you safe!
10400030.mail: Oh, look, mail! Maybe it's from one of my fans!
10400030.feeling3: I need to practice my singing, dancing, and talking skills for my concert! Then I'll have to prepare a stage... Aaahhh, there's so fakking much I need to do!
10400030.lose: ... I'll make up for it at my next concert!

602011.detail: Fixated on my younger sister, hmm? You lend credibility to the adage that heroism breeds virility. Hahah!
602011.touch: Enjoy your time here. Let others take care of any bothersome chores in the meantime.
602011.main: What do you think of this neon-lit cityscape? It doesn't start to compare to the idyllic vistas of Sardegna, but it has its own merits.|You truly are dependable to the utmost, obliging my younger sister with your company like this.|Valiant? I'm not sure where she is. Which is concerning, as I don't believe she's a good swimmer...
602011.unlock: Good evening, Commander. Here to unwind after a day's work, I take it? Even dignitaries desire a bit of luxury sometimes. Hahaha.
602011.drop_descrip: Good evening, Commander. Here to unwind after a day's work, I take it? Even dignitaries desire a bit of luxury sometimes. Hahaha.
602011.home: Is the water temperature satisfactory? You must not come here much, so make the most of your visit. If you want something, just ask for it.

306020.detail: Don't you think... we're bound to be together, Commander? Ahaha.
306020.touch: Commander? We've known each other for so long, you can be a little more forward...
306020.login: Commander, I will ❀always❀ be with you.
306020.battle: You're trying to get between me and the Commander... I'LL KILL YOU!
306020.feeling2: The Marianas? I really... don't like it there...
306020.mission_complete: That was a rich, full day. Now how about we go on a date somewhere?
306020.main: I wonder how I can make you remember, Commander...|Ryuujou... Where have I heard that name before...?|It's not funny anymore! You have to remember, Commander! We've been together ❀since the very beginning❀!
306020.feeling5: No! There's nothing wrong with me! I'm not sick! I'm not! It's just everyone else... why don't you remember!
306020.unlock: Oh, Commander, it's gotten so late. You've kept poor Junyou waiting. Let's go home together, ❀like always❀.
306020.feeling4: Our first time together? I know it was ❀back then❀, but how could you not remember...?
306020.feeling1: Commander, don't tell me you want to break up?!
306020.propose: Commander, you finally remembered... our ❀memories❀ and our ❀promise❀... Ahhh, I'm so touched... Hehe... Well then, just like we promised ❀back then❀...
306020.drop_descrip: Hiyou-class aircraft carrier number two – Junyou.
306020.profile: It's me, Junyou, your oldest friend! After those nasty girls tormented me so much, after all the fighting in the Aleutians, Santa Cruz, the Marianas, I finally got to see you again! I really don't know how you could have forgotten me... but please, hurry up and remember! Eheheh...
306020.touch2: I know exactly what you're thinking, Commander.
306020.mission: Oh, did you want to go on a date with me ❀again❀, Commander? What can I say...
306020.home: I trust you brought my favorite, just ❀like always❀...?
306020.win_mvp: Ahaha, when I feel the Commander's love for me, I can't help but go a bit overboard.
306020.expedition: Hmph, those girls need to learn to read the room...
306020.mail: Commander? Didn't I tell you not to write so many love letters~?
306020.feeling3: I know all your favorite things, Commander.
306020.lose: We lost? What are you saying, Commander? Don't you know Junyou ❀always❀ wins?

205041.detail: Don't be shy, Commander~ Come on, come on over here~ How do you feel? Are my hands too cold?
205041.touch: Commander, could you put some sunscreen on my back?
205041.login: It's so hot... I can't imagine doing any work! Commander, how about we take a cold shower together??
205041.main: Beach volleyball? But I finally got a chance to be intimate with you...I'll PASS~|I'll love whatever gifts you give me!|I'm wiped out. So much swimming! Commander... can you carry me home?
205041.unlock: Even if it's the Commander's gift, wearing it is pretty embarrassing. Commander, want to teach me how to swim?
205041.drop_descrip: Although it's a gift from the Commander, it's still embarrassing to wear this....Commander, do you think you could teach me how to swim?
205041.touch2: How's that? The feeling of a bona-fide Big Seven

107221.detail: Yeah, it should be fine to leave my pet in the dorm... I think?
107221.touch: Do you not get what this paragraph means? Let me have a look.
107221.login: Living in a dorm means I don't have to worry about being late for school.
107221.main: Join a club? Maybe I should... Hmm... Actually, I'm good.|Both studies and missions require your full, undivided attention.|Ugh... This collar is too tight... Why are you staring, Commander?
107221.unlock: So this is my new school, huh? Hmm... gotta put my stuff down first before checking in with the teacher.
107221.drop_descrip: So this is my new school, huh? Hmm... gotta put my stuff down first before checking in with the teacher.
107221.touch2: ...Go to the staff room and explain yourself.
107221.win_mvp: I won by making use of the things I learned. That's all there's to it!

302050.detail: *Cries*... I'm so glad that you're still this gentle with me, Commander...
302050.login: Aaaaaah!!! Commander! Don't scare me like that...
302050.battle: Nothing weird is going to pop out, right?
302050.feeling2: *Cries*... Are ghosts scary because they don't exist in this world?
302050.mission_complete: Mission rewards delivered! I wonder if there's anything good...
302050.main: Torpedoes are truly frightening...|It feels creepy at night without any lights on, don't you think...?|I've seen plenty of things in this world! You won't scare me so easily.
302050.feeling5: You... you're going to protect me from anything that appears? You're... you're just making fun of me again, Commander... I'm not blushing! It's just a little hot...
302050.unlock: Woah! You... you scared me~! Oh, it's you, my Commander! I'm {namecode:48}... You're not here to pick on me, are you?
302050.feeling4: *Cries*... There definitely was something strange there just now! I already said a midnight adventure was a bad idea!
302050.propose: *Cries*... I hope you aren't messing with me, Commander! I'll never feel scared again, as long as you're with me... Can I trust you, Commander?
302050.drop_descrip: Second ship of the {namecode:46}-class light cruisers, {namecode:48}.
302050.profile: Sakura Empire, {namecode:46}-class light cruiser, {namecode:48}, reporting in! I participated in battles at the Lesser Sunda Islands, Solomon Islands, and Guadalcanal. I've fought alongside many famous ships, so you've got to work hard to try and have as good of a reputation as I do!
302050.touch2: Uwa! It's touching me! It's touching me!
302050.mission: Commander, I think you've still got a lot of unfinished work to do.
302050.home: *Cries*... Only you wouldn't pick on me, Commander...
302050.win_mvp: Vi- victory? Commander, how did I do?
302050.expedition: The girls have completed their commissions! I hope they didn't bring anything strange back...
302050.mail: Commander, you've got new mail! I hope there aren't any curses written on them...
302050.feeling3: Ah? A midnight adventure? That... it's not a good idea, is it? No, I'm not afraid!
