107141.touch: Commander, did you want to come up on stage as well?
107141.login: Are you down in the dumps? Well, how about I cheer you up with a little show? ...A magic trick, perhaps?
107141.main: Forget about work for the time being and keep your eyes on the excitement, Commander~♪|And the lucky volunteer is... the Commander! Here, no need to feel embarrassed! Come up onstage and join in on the fun~♪|Next up, the Essex's air show! Feast your eyes on the performance!
107141.unlock: It's showtime! The stage is all set for the performance! Let's enjoy this perfect evening together, Commander~!
107141.drop_descrip: It's showtime! The stage is all set for the performance! Let's enjoy this perfect evening together, Commander~!
107141.touch2: Oh? Commander, everyone's looking at us, you know?
107141.win_mvp: I hope you'll all come back for more! ...Hehe, just kidding~♪
107141.lose: I guess we didn't rehearse enough...

107093.detail: One, don't be blinded by the pursuit of perfection; two, seek harmony in the spacing between ink and paper... Hmm... Does this look right? No, there's something off still... Man, this is hard...
107093.touch: Am I supposed to add another stroke here? I understand. Um... right... here?
107093.login: Happy Lunar New Year! I'll be waiting for your orders!
107093.battle: Attack squadron, ready to scramble! Just like an eagle soaring through the sky!
107093.main: This is a special technique to maneuver the flight deck... Fantastic! At this rate, I'll catch up to Enterprise in no time!|What are those girls doing... Eh? Is that how big brushes normally are?!|Intrepid, see that star right there? That's Mercury, but the Dragon Empery used to call it the "Chenxing." Heheh~
107093.unlock: The Dragon Empery's attire and tools of calligraphy... I see, just wearing this outfit makes me feel more scholarly and artistic! I shall put forth my best effort to prepare for the port's Spring Festival!
107093.drop_descrip: The Dragon Empery's attire and tools of calligraphy... I see, just wearing this outfit makes me feel more scholarly and artistic! I shall put forth my best effort to prepare for the port's Spring Festival!
107093.touch2: Am I supposed to add another stroke here? ...Eek?! Commander?!
107093.win_mvp: How'd you like that! Commander, Enterprise, see that?
107093.expedition: The longer the transport distance, the greater the logistical difficulty. I must extend my gratitude to everyone who works so hard to maintain our supply lines.

900283.login: Milord, milord! What shall we do today?
900283.battle: Everyone, go~! Waaah?! My guns fired on accident!
900283.feeling2: Milord, come play with me! Ah... I forgot to bring stuff to play with... what should we do?
900283.mission_complete: Milord, milord! I've brought the rewards... Oops!
900283.main: Milord, Milord! Waah~! ...Thank you, milord. I have always tipped over easily, but I am used to it now.|Milord, do you want to jog with me? I want to become a little faster.|The vase in the hallway broke... It wasn't me, I swear! It just jumped off right as I walked past it...
900283.feeling5: I know how hard my big sister works, so for her sake, I know that I should allow myself to be happy. That way, I can share my happiness with her. Now that you are here, Milord, I think I'll finally be able to do that. I feel so happy every time I see you!
900283.unlock: Woah! It's Milord! Milord in person! Um... I'm Yamahi-, {namecode:79}! I am pleased to make your acquaintance.
900283.feeling4: Your Majesty, do you know this mask? It's a fox mask used in Kagura. Hehe, I'm actually about to practice my Kagura dance now. Do you want to watch?
900283.feeling1: You're so boring, Milord. I don't want to play with you anymore.
900283.propose: Milord? You're going to give this to me? ...Even though I am slow-footed and far from perfect? Milord, you are far too kind. I love you too.
900283.profile: Um... I'm big sister {namecode:78}'s little sister, {namecode:79}! Neither of us have really had good fortune since we were born, but I've grown up well thanks to big sis! Please don't judge me by my looks... I was once the flagship of the Combined Fleet! Planes...? What are those? Can I eat them?
900283.touch2: Woah! Watch out, Milord! I'm about to fire my main gun!
900283.home: Welcome back, Milord, I made you some tea... Woah! Watch out!
900283.win_mvp: Milord, did you see that? Did you?
900283.expedition: Milord, the girls have returned from commissions!
900283.mail: Milord! Milord! Your mail is here!
900283.feeling3: I love my sister, but she's a bit too quiet sometimes. Milord, I like spending time with you more because you'll play with me!

107091.detail: Even being able to see a small portion of these 2448 miles has been an eye-opening experience. Though I wasn't able to ride from sea to shining sea, what an unforgettable journey it's been!
107091.touch: Phew... Hm? This bottle of water is for me? Thank you very much! I'll help myself then.
107091.login: Commander, have you put on your helmet yet? We're about to get going!
107091.main: Enterprise advised me to pursue some hobbies that aren't related to combat... This should count as one of those. |Combat is something that must be done at full throttle. It'd be dangerous to do that while riding though... |You followed us the entire way? What an incredible eagle!
107091.unlock: I'm not trying to go anywhere in particular; I just want to enjoy the scenery along the way. Commander, let's go experience the thrills of the road together.
107091.drop_descrip: I'm not trying to go anywhere in particular; I just want to enjoy the scenery along the way. Commander, let's go experience the thrills of the road together.
107091.touch2: Commander, could you be... too tired to know what you're doing? I knew we should have stopped to rest...
107091.home: Did you want to rest for a bit? That's fine, take your time.

103141.detail: Jazz, rock 'n' roll, or whatever else, you name it and we'll play it!
103141.touch: You already wasted, Puddin'? Tsk, tsk. That's not gonna fly~
103141.login: Welcome to my place, Puddin'! Don't be shy now, get hella jiggy with it!
103141.main: C'mon, Minneapolis! Forget about hunting for a minute and just drink!|Have yourself some snacks before I decide to eat 'em all, Puddin'.|nil|Listen, Puddin', I need party activity ideas! Do we play a game, or put something on?
103141.unlock: Music! Lights! Refreshments! We're all set! Welcome to San Francisco's party! Come and enjoy yourself!
103141.drop_descrip: Music! Lights! Refreshments! We're all set! Welcome to San Francisco's party! Enjoy yourself!
103141.touch2: Okay, you've had WAY too much to drink.
103141.home: You didn't bail on me to go have fun on your own... right? No? All good then~
103141.win_mvp: Now that's a clean victory! Lemme see a big smile, c'mon! Ahaha!

302051.detail: A-all those Halloween monsters are just people in costumes, right?! ... There aren't any real ones roaming around, right?!
302051.touch: You make me feel safer than anyone else, Commander...
302051.login: C-C-C-Commander! Trick or... o-or... I can't do it...!
302051.main: Monsters aren't real... Monsters aren't real... M-m-monsters aren't real....!|W-w-why do they make even the pumpkins look scary?!|L-l-looks like everyone's enjoying Halloween... I-I-I-I'm not shuddering, okay?!
302051.feeling5: If only I could board the pumpkin carriage and meet the prince of my... What?! Commander, h-how long have you been here?! D-don't stare at my face! *Sob*...
302051.unlock: There's many monsters roaming around during Halloween... B-but I'm not scared, okay?! ... Umm, err, uh... Can I hold your hand?
302051.drop_descrip: There's many monsters roaming around during Halloween... B-but I'm not scared, okay?! ... Umm, err, uh... Can I hold your hand?
302051.touch2: *Eeek*?! I-I'll turn you into a frog!

107090.detail: What would you like to know, Commander? I'll answer to the best of my abilities.
107090.touch: Time to sortie?! Just leave it to me! Oh... you just wanted to chat...?
107090.login: There you are. I've already finished preparing everything. Commander, give us your orders!
107090.battle: All carrier-based aircraft in position, anti-air defense preparations complete. All forces, full speed ahead!
107090.feeling2: I witnessed the end of the era of battleships with my own eyes. Will carriers share the same fate some day...?
107090.mission_complete: The mission rewards have arrived. Are you sure you don't need me to go get it?
107090.main: Everyone knows that the Essex class is strong, but still, Enterprise is all they ever talk about... *sigh*... |There are a lot of ships in my class. As the nameship, I have to do everything I can to be a good role model... |Musashi and Yamato? They were... yes, formidable rivals worthy of respect. I hope I can meet them again one day.
107090.feeling5: I might never be able to become a hero like Enterprise... But when I'm with you, I feel like I can do so much more than just that...
107090.upgrade: When will I be able to get jets...
107090.unlock: So this is where Enterprise is... A-ahem! I am Essex, one of the Union's state-of-the-art aircraft carriers. Commander, you can expect great things from me! I swear that I won't disappoint you!
107090.feeling4: I won't lose to anyone, not even to Enterprise. But how do I get everyone to acknowledge this? Commander, if you were in my shoes, what would you do?
107090.feeling1: I wonder how Enterprise puts up with someone like you...
107090.propose: Once you've experienced the happiness of two people supporting each other, it becomes something you can't live without. Thank you, Commander. I no longer have to walk alone in my quest to prove my worth. I promise to always be at your side, wherever you go.
107090.drop_descrip: Essex-class aircraft carrier – Essex, Hull Number CV-9.
107090.profile: I am the nameship of the Essex-class carriers. Although I was built with great expectations, I was always overshadowed by Enterprise's success. If only I could have been deployed sooner...
107090.mission: There are still unfinished missions? Mind letting me handle things this time...?
107090.home: The fleet has safely returned. Commander, I've prepared the battle report for you. Time is of the essence, so please review it right away.
107090.win_mvp: Enterprise, did you see my feat?
107090.expedition: The birth of the Essex-class would not have been possible without the hard work of the logistics teams. I have to show my gratitude to everyone.
107090.mail: There's new mail for you. Here you go.
107090.feeling3: Jealousy? No, that's not the case. Enterprise is a true hero worthy of all the respect she gets. However, compared to her dazzling aura, I'm just...
107090.lose: I won't let it end like this... I swear it!

107037.detail: Actually, I didn't throw together this picnic all by myself. My new friend helped a whole bunch~
107037.touch: Hey, you've got food stuck on your cheek, Commander. Come over here and I'll wipe it off for you.
107037.login: Hehe, you're right on time! And that earns you a prize! Come and have a slice of Sister's whole-grain toast! Get it while it's still hot~
107037.main: Tomato and veggie sandwiches with whole-grain bread! Today's lunch menu is super healthy!|Ah, hold on, you have to wash your hands before eating! Commander, you too!|You're welcome to lie down over there and take a nap, but~ I can't guarantee that you won't have circles and squiggles drawn all over your face when you wake up~ Heehee~
107037.unlock: Tada! Welcome to Sister Sara's special picnic! Look at all the delicious food I brought~ See, Commander, I told you it wasn't just another prank~♪
107037.drop_descrip: Tada! Welcome to Sister Sara's special picnic! Look at all the delicious food I brought~ See, Commander, I told you it wasn't just another prank~♪
107037.touch2: Woooah! ...I'm confiscating your food! You've made Sister Sara very angry! Hmph!
107037.home: C-Commander! There's a caterpillar on your shoulder! Just kidding~ Did I spook ya?

207030.detail: Could you help me pick up that handkerchief...? I'd lose my balance if I try to pick it up myself...
207030.touch: It's as though... I've received your recognition, Commander. I feel so relieved.
207030.login: Greetings, Commander. I've tidied up a bit here. What do you think?
207030.feeling2: Commander, what do you find most important in a girl? Seriously, could you look me in the eyes when we're speaking?
207030.mission_complete: Don't forget to collect your rewards, Commander!
207030.main: Have you seen where did I put my planes? Oh? Right in front of me? Sorry, something blocked my line of sight.| Commander... can you feel my heartbeat through the palm of your hand?|Commander, why are you always staring at me? Am I that pretty?
207030.feeling5: No matter what you ask of me, Commander, I'll accept it... So, Commander, please tell me how you feel about me.
207030.upgrade: This way we can radiate our brilliance even further.
207030.unlock: Greetings, Commander! Aircraft carrier Illustrious reporting in! I pray that you will bring love and peace to this world. May the light be with you.
207030.feeling4: Commander... do you want to try... a soft landing?
207030.feeling1: Not even my light can reach the darkness within your heart?
207030.propose: Even though light should be shared equally among us all, it's fine for you to have a bit more. After all, I've received something important from the Commander as well.
207030.drop_descrip: Illustrious-class aircraft carrier – Illustrious, Hull Number 87!
207030.profile: Greetings, Commander. I am the armored aircraft carrier Illustrious. I may seem gentle, but I have quite the temper. I single-handedly bullied the Italian fleet during the raid at Taranto.
207030.touch2: Seriously, Commander, you're like a little kid.
207030.mission: Commander, it's no good to leave missions unfinished.
207030.home: Feeling tired? Relax for a while. How about a massage?
207030.win_mvp: The light shines upon our land of triumph.
207030.expedition: The light shall disperses the fog of darkness. Oh? The girls are back!
couple_encourage: How's Saratoga doing these days?
May the light illuminate Kaede's Legion!
207030.mail: Here's your mail, Commander! Should I open it for you?
207030.feeling3: Commander, while I'm like this, I take a special liking towards suprise night attacks. Seriously, I didn't mean it like that, but is the Commander into things like that?
207030.lose: Let's retreat, lest I lose my life...

107065.detail: Right, I didn't get to ask you earlier since you were in a hurry, but what do you think about my outfit? I value your input just as much as I value that of Hornet and the others.
107065.login: I'm Enterprise of the Eagle Union. Let's proceed to the event venue.
107065.main: I see, so this is how it's done. Next time, I'll have to learn how to make... Hm? Ahh, I was talking about ice cream. Do you want some, Commander? |I'm used to emergency sorties. Even if I'm at a banquet, just give me the order and I'll scramble my planes.|What about Independence? Ahh, she's a nice and adorable girl, just like Eagle. Good friends who heal my heart from the weariness of battle.
107065.unlock: My ballgown? I don't normally get to wear clothes like these, so it took me a while to change. Ah, let's hurry to the venue. We shouldn't keep everyone else waiting.
107065.drop_descrip: My ballgown? I don't normally get to wear clothes like these, so it took me a while to change. Ah, let's hurry to the venue. We shouldn't keep everyone else waiting.
107065.home: Commander, you shouldn't overexert yourself... Hm, you should be the one saying that to me? I understand.
107065.win_mvp: May this victory serve as the ornament to a fine celebration.
107065.expedition: The girls in the commission fleet have returned? The formalities will have to wait then. I'll go welcome them back first.

107064.detail: I do not believe that it is correct to wantonly resort to violence, even in the name of justice.
107064.touch: Commander, do you need me for something?
107064.login: Good day, Commander. There's still some time until the strategy meeting, so you should rest up while you still have the opportunity to.
107064.battle: Enterprise, sallying forth! Let us crush our enemies!
107064.main: I'm quite impressed by the Royal Maids. Aside from their combat prowess, they're also very good at a wide variety of other things. |Vestal, what's the matter? ...No, I've been making sure to eat! Commander has been making all sorts... I mean, I cook from time to time as well! |My eagle is quite attached to you, Commander. We should all get along just like you two. Hehe.
107064.unlock: There is no doubt in my mind that I was born to fight. For the azure lanes of liberty, Enterprise, engaging!
107064.drop_descrip: There is no doubt in my mind that I was born to fight. For the azure lanes of liberty, Enterprise, engaging!
107064.touch2: You wouldn't do this to Yorktown, would you...
107064.mission: We still have missions that haven't been completed. You should check on their progress.
107064.home: Commander, thank you for your hard work. Let's get ready for the next operation.
107064.win_mvp: Our slight advantage seems to have given us the victory here.
107064.expedition: Would you like to greet the commission fleet? It's a good idea to get some exercise. Otherwise, Hornet's going to make fun of you.

306030.detail: You're like a kid sometimes, Commander... Come over here~
306030.touch: Are you looking for me, Commander?
306030.login: Commander, have you eaten yet? No? Let me make something for you. You can't head to work without first preparing your body and mind!
306030.battle: I'm not very skilled in real combat... but I shall not betray your expectations!
306030.hp_warning: Looks like I can't afford to take it easy just yet.
306030.feeling2: Want to take a nap, Commander?
306030.mission_complete: Commander is sure forgetful, always needing my reminder just to claim the rewards.
306030.main: Having long legs isn't necessarily a good thing. A high center of mass makes it easy to tip over...|Commander, I prepared some snacks for us. Do you want to relax for a while?|It's amazing to see how much my younger sisters have accomplished, but sometimes it makes me a bit sad to see everything they've gone through...
306030.feeling5: Commander, the moon is beautiful tonight, isn't it? I've prepared some drinks... would you like to stargaze together? I wouldn't do this for anyone else - this is a special service just for you, my dear.
306030.upgrade: Now I can help you even more, Commander!
306030.unlock: Ah, it's the Commander... My name is Houshou, and I'll be in your care from now on. Please leave the children of the fleet in my care. I won't let you down!
306030.feeling4: A prominent person once praised my beauty, but to be honest, I am not so sure about myself. But if Commander was to acknowledge me, perhaps I could find my confidence. So... Commander, am I beautiful?
306030.propose: My dream is to one day settle down with the person I love and open a small bar somewhere... Now, it doesn't seem like my dream is so distant anymore. Right, my dear?
306030.profile: I guess you could say that I was the first aircraft carrier ever in the world. You could call me the eldest sister, or mother, of them all! Feel free to consult with me whenever you'd like, Commander. I'm always here for you.
306030.touch2: Ahh! ... Commander, that's naughty. You can't touch me there.
306030.mission: You've got new missions, Commander. Care for a challenge this time?
306030.home: Good work, Commander! Would you like dinner? A bath? Or perhaps... a drink first? Hehe~!
306030.expedition: Commander, your girls have returned from commission. I'll welcome them back now, but you should hurry over as well.
306030.feeling3: I look a bit like a courtesan? Hehe~ Well then, mister, it seems like tonight shall be our one and only night together. Let us feel the warmth of our embrace, then let the memories fade to nothing. How does that sound?

107062.detail: Being able to enjoy this peaceful, festive holiday atmosphere is only possible because of everyone's continued hard work... Right, Commander?
107062.touch: Commander, it seems that this coat is big enough to accommodate two people. It's super warm - want to see for yourself?
107062.login: Lanterns... should be hung up like this, right? Ah, Commander, you're here. I heard that they hang lanterns up to celebrate Lunar New Year in the Dragon Empery, so I gave it a try... You think it's fine? Festive, isn't it?
107062.main: My flight deck is also decorated with a theme from the Dragon Empery. Its colors represent joy and happiness. Not bad, huh. |According to legend, a mythical beast called the "Nian" comes out during the Lunar New Year. It can be warded off by setting off a lot of firecrackers. |I heard that it's customary in the Dragon Empery to hand out "red envelopes" during the New Year. Should I prepare some for the Union girls?
107062.unlock: So this is the traditional attire of the Dragon Empery? Hmm... it fits quite well. Oh? Custom-made bow and arrows… Interesting, let's see how far these arrows can fly.
107062.drop_descrip: So this is the traditional attire of the Dragon Empery? Hmm... it fits quite well. Oh? Custom-made bow and arrows… Interesting, let's see how far these arrows can fly.
107062.home: There's no harm in taking a little break before the next battle, Commander.

302052.detail: My sisters wanted to dress up as Santa Claus and go around handing presents to kids... I didn't go with them because I'm not good with the dark.
302052.touch: Are... you trying to share my body heat?
302052.login: Two people sitting in front of the fireplace like this... feels a bit like family.
302052.main: It's so cozy right next to the fireplace... There are even fuzzy Manjuus to cuddle~ |Um... Commander, what kind of presents should I give to everyone? |I've already done my research. There are no ghost stories or anything of the sort related to Christmas... R-right, Commander?
302052.feeling5: I'm not really sure how Christmas should be celebrated. But just sitting next to you in front of the fireplace like this... is probably fine. Commander, i-it's a bit cold... I'd like to get a little closer...
302052.unlock: Commander? I only came here to help wrap up all the presents for tomorrow, n-not because the fireplace is too cozy and I don't want to get up...
302052.drop_descrip: Commander? I only came here to help wrap up all the presents for tomorrow, n-not because the fireplace is too cozy and I don't want to get up...
302052.touch2: I knew it! You were trying to take advantage of me!
302052.home: I was told that this outfit would be good for wearing around the house, but it's a bit too loose... S-stop staring at me already.

201320.detail: I was just looking for you, Commander! Let's do something fun.
201320.touch: What's up, Commander? Time I get to work? All right, time I get to work!
201320.login: Commander, you kept me waiting so long I got mad and took apart your chair! Wh-what if I can't put it back together...?
201320.hp_warning: It's not time to retreat yet!
201320.feeling2: My outfit? It's different because I served in some pretty frigid waters back in the day~ Heheh, it's pretty cool though, huh? What do you think?
201320.mission_complete: Commander, here's all the mission rewards. Take a look at them already!
201320.main: Commander, let's build an igloo when it snows! I'm pretty good at those!|Yippeeee! Yahoooo! Ah, Commander, errr~ Why am I horsing around like this? Just bored, I guess.|All right, target acquired: daydreaming Commander. Eskimo head smasher! GO!
201320.feeling5: I've been good? Eheheh, that's all thanks to you, Commander. Since you've been giving me so much attention, I don't need to bother anyone else. I can just wait until you have time for me. Riiight?
201320.unlock: Eskimo, Tribal-class Destroyer, is here! Oi, this fleet's not half bad! Nice to meet you, Commander!
201320.feeling4: Too noisy? Hmm, well, I'm just trying to get your attention. Everyone's really... Oh no, could I be bothering someone? I'd better go apologize!
201320.feeling1: You're no fun at all, Commander...
201320.propose: All right, I promise, Commander. I'll work hard, and be good. I won't cause any more trouble! Just keep on giving me more attention! Eheheh!
201320.skill: All right! Have a taste of this!
201320.profile: I'm Tribal-class Destroyer Eskimo! During the war, I mostly served in the Home Fleet. I defeated Z19 at the Battle of Narvik, but then Z2 struck back at me... After that, I did good work in the Mediterranean.
201320.mission: A new mission? All right, a new mission!
201320.home: I finished all the work you left here for me.
201320.win_mvp: Yes! I'm the MVP! Now cheer for me!
201320.expedition: The commission team's back? I'll go get them!
couple_encourage: Hey! Z2, you'd better make Z1 behave!
201320.mail: Commander, I got the mail for you~ Heh heh. It was nothing. Don't mention it.
201320.feeling3: Y-you saw my room? Well, when I get too bored, I end up taking apart the furniture... and then I don't know how to put it back together. But why, though?

107049.detail: C-Commander?! I-I-Is my bridge, really that beautiful?
107049.touch: Yeah yeah, Commander is totally not good without a Teacher here... Yup, can't help it~
107049.login: This child seems fine... This one is recovering well... Ah, welcome back, Commander!
107049.battle: Everyone, it's time to put what you learned to use!
107049.main: A weapon may be powerful, but if it can't be used properly, it won't be completely effective. It is the teacher's job to teach you how to use them! Physical education? I-I'll teach that again!|I've only improved a few times before, and they were just small enhancements. Now that everyone is stronger, I can start getting some work done.|Commander? I believe in you, so I'm letting you study on your own while I work on my planes. I'll get angry if you avoid your study this time, alright?
107049.unlock: The modernization that had never happened has finally been completed! From now on, I, Ms. Ranger, will continue to teach as well~
107049.drop_descrip: I didn't realize I could still become more powerful! I'll work harder from here on out to teach everyone how to fight!
107049.touch2: Commander, can you help a teacher out here a little?... Eeek! ....Really?...
107049.home: Commander, you've grown but you haven't changed much. Alright, here's your reward~
107049.win_mvp: If you engage in some special training with me, you'll withstand fatigue for a longer time, Commander! ...Eh? Why are you looking at me like that?

301015.detail: If my sisters saw me working hard... would they say something like "Fubuki's such a hard-working role model?" Ehe... ehehe... Ah, I'm so so sorry, I just spaced out for a bit!
301015.touch: Commander, this bell is just for decoration...
301015.login: Commander... Err, I mean, welcome! What would you like to order~?
301015.main: Sigh... When will I be able to handle this job as easily as Miss Belfast does?|You want to chat with me? Sure, as soon as I get finished with all this stuff... Ughh...|Did someone call for me? Excuse me, I'll be right there! Oh hey, it's Akatsuki and the others!
301015.unlock: Welcome, welcome! Oh, Commander! I've actually started working here part-time, but I'm still learning— Wooah?! Phew... Th-that was a close one...
301015.drop_descrip: Welcome, welcome! Oh, Commander! I've actually started working here part-time, but I'm still learning— Wooah?! Phew... Th-that was a close one...
301015.touch2: Eep?! It's hard to keep my balance, so stop with that already!
301015.home: This Oxy-cola goes to this table, and uhh, a few more minutes on this pizza, and umm... Ahhh! This would be so much easier with a clone of me here!

308011.detail: I should make some friends? But I don't need any~! You're the only person I need!
308011.touch: Hehehe~ Do you wanna walk to and from school with me?
308011.login: School's so boring... I'd rather be by your side, Commander~ Hehehe~
308011.main: Eek! The wind nearly... Hmm? Were you trying to sneak a peek~?|Commander, help me with my extra lessons...|Do you like my outfit, Commander? Is it cute? Hehehe~
308011.unlock: Aww, do I have to go to school? ... Oh, Commander! Are you here to see me off?
308011.drop_descrip: Aww, do I have to go to school? ... Oh, Commander! Are you here to see me off?
308011.touch2: No touching until everyone else has gone home...
308011.mail: Mail? I hope it's not an angry letter from some teacher...

301370.detail: Commander, I haven't pranked you just yet.

103010.feeling1: Hey, Commander, this isn't OK at all.

103010.drop_descrip: Pensacola-class Heavy Cruiser – Pensacola, Hull Number CA-24!
103010.skill: Main guns: OK! Armor: OK! We're doing this!
103010.profile: OKOK, self-introduction time, right? I'm Pensacola, I have a little sister named Salt Lake City… Uh, what else do I even say when introducing myself? I helped out Hornet and Yorktown, but there's not much to say about that… Oh well, anyway, let me handle everything and it'll be OK!
103010.touch2: H-hey, that's not at all what this gesture means!

103010.expedition: Hey, a commission's been completed! ... It's not OK to just ignore those hardworking girls, you hear?
103010.mail: I've got your mail... here! Here you go, Commander.
103010.feeling3: Are we going out? OK, I'll let you decide where we're going. I'm fine with going anywhere, so just pick whatever you want!
103010.lose: Damn... This isn't OK at all...

107030.mission_complete: This is bad, Commander! The mission rewards are missing! --Darn, you caught me.
107030.main: Boo! Hehe, did I susprise you?  Commander, you're slow, aren't you?!|Commander, don't confuse me with my big sister!|Eh? Call you 'big bro'? There's no way that's happening~
107030.feeling5: Commander, you dropped something~~ *kiss* ...Hehe, it was my heart♡. Here, you can keep it!
107030.unlock: Hey there, and good day, Commander! I am Lexington...'s little sister, Saratoga~ If there's nothing important, I'm leaving now
107030.feeling4: Commander, I have something I want to tell you. I'm gonna write it on the back of your hand~ and done... Did you think I'm gonna write 'I like you'? Silly Commander~
107030.feeling1: Pranks? I already stopped pulling them on you~ You're no fun for those
107030.propose: Ah, Commander. Please wait for a bit~ The Eagle Union carriers are all gathering~ Eh? This is a once in a lifetime occassion! Despite my appearance I am a veteran. I'm well respected!
107030.drop_descrip: Lexington-class aircraft carrier ー Saratoga, Hull Number CV-3!
107030.skill: Where are you looking? I'm right over here~
107030.profile:
I am aircraft carrier Lexington's little sister, Saratoga! Hmm... I like to play pranks! But you already knew that, Commander~ 
Pioneer of aviation tactics? If my sister hadn't passed away so soon, that title would've definitely been hers.
107030.mission: Commander, can't you complete even a mission?
107030.win_mvp: Ooh la la~ Big sis is busy, so it's fine that I get to come by once a while~
107030.expedition: Commander, my patrol planes told me the girls out for commission have returned~
couple_encourage: Double Lexington Trouble!
Cute li'l Saratoga isn't some "Old Brother"~
How come you've all grown so much?!
Let's go! Time to make breaking news!
Heheheh~ Can you figure out who's the real deal? ♪
Let's do our best as Virtual Idols, Sandy!
107030.mail: You didn't see the mail? --Then should I read it?
107030.feeling3: Commander, what's the greatest difference between me and my big sister? The answer, is my 'color' today!
107030.lose: Oh dang~ I'll go back for repairs, and then have a good rest while I'm at it~

107021.touch: Commander, do you like my dress that much? Should we ask the Empery girls to tailor an outfit for you as well?
107021.login: Welcome back, Commander. Are you well acquainted with the customs of the Dragon Empery? Then, why don't you tell me a bit about their New Year? I'm quite curious~
107021.main: An idol will change her outfits and dresses several times during a performance, each one bringing forth a different character... As long as I can bring smiles to everyone's faces, I will be happy. |nil|Wearing this outfit seems to have gotten the children all fired up~ Hehe, Commander, don't you think this outfit brings out my domestic side?
107021.feeling5: In the Dragon Empery, the New Year symbolizes joy and reuniting with family. Commander, just being together with you and all the children in the port right now, counts as a "family reunion," doesn't it? Hehe~
107021.unlock: Hehe… sometimes you can completely change the way people see you with just a simple change in attire. Don't you agree, Commander~? Don’t worry, I'm still your Lexington~
107021.drop_descrip: Hehe… sometimes you can completely change the way people see you with just a simple change in attire. Don't you agree, Commander~? Don’t worry, I'm still your Lexington~
107021.home: A well-fought battle, Commander. Why don't you come try my Lexington-style East-West fusion cooking?
107021.win_mvp: Hehe, new outfits do bring new joys with them after all~

107010.detail: Commander, you're staring at me... Are you ready to answer my questions?
107010.touch: Please do not treat me like a child~! I am a teacher! TEA-CHER!
107010.login: Commander, I'll assist you with your work the best I can!
107010.battle: This is the chance to show me what you learned. Do it properly!
107010.feeling2: What are you doing, sleeping in the job?! Take you tutoring seriously!
107010.mission_complete: The reward for diligence has been delivered. Keep it up for next time!
107010.main: Commander! ~Hey, you could've done better than this. Why are you not serious about this...?|At this rate nothing about the fleet will change! Get yourself together, Commander!|Commander? Are you listening? I'm gonna throw the chalk at you~! I hate people who don't listen to me! Hmph!
107010.feeling5: I, Ms. Langley, do not mix personal and work lives! If you think that I'll give you special treatment just because of our relationship, you are sorely mistaken! ... B-but in private, I'm fine with that!
107010.upgrade: Even when you become stronger, never forget about why you had to in the first place.
107010.unlock: I've been newly assigned to assist you. Name's Langley. You listening? I am going to fix what's wrong with you, and put you on the right track to running a fleet.
107010.feeling4: There's nothing more for me to teach you-- What? Teach you about myself? Y-You idiot!... Ugh
107010.feeling1: I never thought that there would be a student I cannot teach... It seems better for me to quit...
107010.propose: I was concerned about whether Commander takes good care of himself before...so from now on, teacher Langley will also correct issues of your personal life; Don't even think about running away, Commander~
107010.drop_descrip: Langley-class aicraft carrier ー Langley, Hull Number CV-1!
107010.skill: Commander, pay close attention to my moves!
107010.profile: Ahem! I am the Eagle Union's first, I repeat, the first aircraft carrier, Langley! I do not think highly of my own fighting ability, but I've put out numerous outstanding pilots! The Eagle Union's aircraft carrier begins with me, I say!
107010.touch2: *phone call* Hello, is this the military police? Yes, it's the same place and the same person...
107010.mission: Erhmm... Have you finished your homework today?
107010.home: Commander, where are you heading? It's time for a reflection meeting
107010.win_mvp: Got it, everyone? Maintain this pace, alright?
107010.expedition: The girls on the commission field trip have returned. Now, go and check their progress.
107010.mail: Check your mail periodically. It's a good habit!
107010.feeling3: You seem to be getting better at this- Eh? It's thanks to me? Ah, well... y-you're welcome...
107010.lose: *sobs* ... I'm not qualified as a teacher... Maybe I should go back to transporting coal...

106551.detail: Getting the choreography down isn't the hard part. It's being able to cheer so enthusiastically like Reno... It's a bit too embarrassing if you ask me...
106551.touch: Is this towel for me? Ah, thank you very much, Commander.
106551.login: Cheerleaders raise the morale of the players. It doesn't seem much different from the role of an escort carrier, supporting those who are working hard on the battlefield.
106551.main: Captain Reno, I think your enthusiasm is nothing but commendable, but wouldn't it be better to take a break now to conserve our energy? |Commander, I brought some water and sports drinks. Feel free to take whatever you want. |Even though this squad was thrown together last minute, thanks to the support of you and Craven, I don't want to lose to the other factions!
106551.unlock: Phew... Can't train hard if you don't stay hydrated! Oh, Commander, good day! Did you come to watch us practice?
106551.drop_descrip: Phew... Can't train hard if you don't stay hydrated! Oh, Commander, good day! Did you come to watch us practice?
106551.touch2: Commander, you seem to be quite good at taking advantage of these situations...
106551.home: The actual meet is coming up... I've got to practice even harder!

107036.login: Surprise snowball shower! Hehehe~ I'd say that was a chilling success! Feeling awake now, Commander?

107036.unlock: Tadaaah! Happy Lunar New Year, Commander! How do you like this fresh new spring look that Sara's rocking? Hope you haven't forgotten our promise to check out the port's spring festival together~ Ready, then? Let's go!
107036.drop_descrip: Tadaaah! Happy Lunar New Year, Commander! How do you like this fresh new spring look that Sara's rocking? Hope you haven't forgotten our promise to check out the port's spring festival together~ Ready, then? Let's go!

105120.detail: Being stared like that makes a bit shy...
105120.touch: Do you need help with something?

105120.feeling2: Commander remembers me~ Not that I’m boasting or anything, but I still have confidence in my low sense of existence. (smiles wryly)

105120.main: What do I wear inside? It's not something that’s so significant |If I think about it, I certainly have been to many places... seen many landscapes, and also parted ways with many people. |Sometimes I get so envious of my younger sister Washington and how she’s so energetic all the time.

105120.upgrade: I'll try to work a bit harder~

105120.drop_descrip: North Carolina class battleship— North Carolina, hull number BB-55.

105120.mission: It’s not good to leave tasks unfinished.

105120.lose: Not so successful... let's try again next time.

106019.detail: Hmm? This outfit is more refreshing so, no issues!

106019.drop_descrip: Commander~ I am Long Island~ I've changed? Ghosts don't cha... Huh? I seemed to have become a little more alive!

808010.battle: They're just slightly bigger targets! On y va!

808010.main: You appointed me as your secretary because you were so enamored with my gorgeous body, weren't you? Spot on, aren't I~? 808010.propose: So, you wanna chain Surcouf to your side with this ring? Jeez, aren't you greedy~ But, since it's you... I might be fine with it♪
808010.profile: Submarine Surcouf of Iris Libre, that's who I am. "Cruiser submarine"? Ah, are you talking about my gorgeous body which matches that of a cruiser~? Well, my firepower matches that of a cruiser, too! I bump into people quite a lot, but don't worry about that. Hahaha♪
808010.touch2: Commander, if you wanna fondle 'em, just say so first~
808010.mission: Okay, let's see what rewards we got today!
808010.home: Commander, did you bring anything for me?
808010.win_mvp: *Yawn*... Winning makes me sleepy, somehow... Mmh...
808010.expedition: Commander, a commission's been completed~ I'll go check if they found anything neato♪
808010.mail: Commander, you've got new mail! ... Huh? No, I didn't bring it with me. I'm just saying you should go get it~
808010.feeling3: Salut~! Wanna go have some fun, Commander? Let's take a walk around town, go shopping, then fall asleep in a grass field~
808010.lose: Oops, we lost... Commander, think we should flee?

305024.drop_descrip: Milord, Milord, welcome to the store! Yamashiro is a sales clerk today! Mhm, I'll do my best!

401231.detail: Have you memorized this? This part's going to show up on the test. If you don't pass, you'll...

401231.main: Commander, do you remember the naval intelligence I explained to you earlier? ... I'm asking you a question here... |Afterwards, let's get something to eat. It's on me. Consider it a reward for all your hard work today. |Commander, pain is temporary. Victory is forever.

401231.drop_descrip: This is going to be on the exam! If you don't take thorough notes, I am going to punish you!

105190.detail: Tell me when you're done inspecting.
105190.touch: You want someone to pamper you? ... You want ME to?
105190.login: For lunch, I'll make... Oh, Commander, are you going for a stroll?
105190.battle: Pretty tough, aren't you? You won't cry if I hit you, will you?
105190.hp_warning: ... So you want me to get serious?
105190.feeling2: How to get stronger? Uhh, do some push-ups? ... Not working for you?

Umm... when I was in Casablanca, I fought a battleship who held out a long time even with just a single turret... I'd like to fight her again in her finished state.
105190.feeling5: I don't have any dreams. But I have the power to grant them. Commander, do you have a dream for me to grant one day?
105190.unlock: Hm? Ah... my turn to speak. I'm Massachusetts. I'm just a regular old South Dakota-class you can find anywhere... So, yeah, I hope we can... get along.
105190.feeling4: I like how cool you look when you're pushing yourself hard... but overdoing it isn't good. I'll force you to rest if I have to.
105190.feeling1: Your body is weak, Commander. Are you eating properly?
105190.propose: Umm, yeah... I already know what you want to do and want to say... Because I love you too, Commander.
105190.drop_descrip: South Dakota-class battleship – Massachusetts, Hull Number BB-59.
105190.profile: I guess I'm the most normal ship in my class. I earned 11 battle stars, which is less than South Dakota did. "I hardly suffered any damage"? That's cause I never fought anyone strong enough... Here's hoping that I'll get to fight as hard as my sister did back then.
105190.touch2: ... If you'd move your body more, you'd have fewer weird thoughts.
105190.mission: So many missions waiting on us...
105190.home: You're back... Did you get hurt? If anyone pokes fun at you, we can talk about it.
105190.win_mvp: It's over already? But I was just warming up... Aren't there any other enemies left?
105190.expedition: ... Oh, look. They've brought so much back. I'll go help them out.
couple_encourage: The way you are now... I like it. This is good.
I envy your defense, sis...
105190.mail: I'll leave your letter here. Check it later.
105190.feeling3: Seeing you challenging yourself with things you can't do is... interesting. It makes me want to explore my own limits, too.

108031.detail: Some snacks for Albacore and a torpedo model kit for Dace... These convenience stores really have everything, don't they!
108031.touch: No, Commander! You can't have my precious discounted chips!
108031.login: I've been waiting for you, Commander!
108031.main: IT'S A SUPER RARE! Holy mackerel! Commander, look! Hehehe~ See what I just got?!|I snagged myself a limited-edition Sara plushie! Aren't you jealous~? ... Y-you already own one? D-did they scam me?!|School life is a lot more fun than I expected! I might just be a natural scholar!
108031.unlock: You're late, Commander! ... What's all this? Heheh, it's loot I got from the stop n' rob's bargain bin! Here, have some bread!
108031.drop_descrip: You're late, Commander! ... What's all this? Heheh, it's loot I got from the stop n' rob's bargain bin! Here, have some bread!
108031.touch2: I bet you waited for me to leave school just to do that!
108031.mission: A mission? Is that my homework?
108031.expedition: A-are they the fabled Fantastic Forty Percent Off?! ... Oh, it's just the commission team.

203060.detail: My big sister is definitely cuter, at least compared to me.
203060.touch: So, Commander, you think I'm actually a bit too big?
203060.login: Welcome back~ What are we going to do today?
203060.battle: I'll do my best to not embarrass my sister!
203060.hp_warning: This is a bit of a struggle...
203060.feeling2: It's not an exaggeration to say my sister is a world treasure, a gift from the heavens. It's an honor for me to have a sister like her.
203060.mission_complete: Here are your rewards! Please take good care of them.
203060.main: Is it not common knowledge that my big sister is the cutest in the world?| For allowing me to use the intel my sister gave me, Bismarck is such a generous person.|If it's about my sister, I could speak for three days and three nights and still not be done.
203060.feeling5: Though we speak of it, I've never thought I would such a day would come... How should I react?... Commander, can you teach me?
203060.upgrade: I'll continue to do my best, with my big sister as my goal~
203060.unlock: Hello, I'm Norfolk's little sister, Dorsetshire~! I look more mature than my sister? Surely you jest! She's my role model!
203060.feeling4: Ah, could it be that you've developed feelings beyond friendship for me? In that case I must properly respond to them.
203060.feeling1: I really can't compare to my sister...
203060.propose: You sure are a weird person, Commander. To chase after me who is but a tiny star to the bright moon that is my sister. But I too am attracted to you, if you are okay with someone like me then I would be happy to accept.
203060.drop_descrip:
Norfolk-class heavy cruiser, Dorsetshire, Hull Number 40
<color=#ffde38>Unlock build after receiving</color>
203060.skill: Sister, please lend me your strength!
203060.profile: The offshoot of the County-class, the Norfolk-class, includes me and my sisters. My proudest achievement was giving chase to Bismarck and not letting my sister's intel go to waste. I am still far from matching her, so I must become a sister she can be proud of!
203060.mission: Missions, huh? Makes me think of all the time I spent with my sister.
203060.home: Good work, Commander! Come, sit and have some tea. I will tell you some things about my sister~
203060.win_mvp: This gets me one step closer to my big sister~
203060.expedition: Ah, the commission team is back~! Commander, could you let me go on a commission with my sister next time?
203060.feeling3: I'm fine the way I am? Aha, you really know how to give compliments, Commander. Compared to my sister though, I'm still but an ugly duckling.

401250.detail: Mr. Anchor, what must I do to become as outstanding as my sister...?
401250.touch: Zzz.... woah! Sorry, I shouldn't have been daydreaming...
401250.login: You're right on time. Well then, I should also get fired up.
401250.battle: Z25, currently searching for enemy ships!
401250.hp_warning: I can hang on a bit longer...

401250.feeling5: Ehehe... Haah, it's still no good. Mr. Anchor, sorry for making you act like the commander and practice with me for so long. I give up... just being like this should be good enough... Eh... w-wait... Commander?
401250.upgrade: Becoming stronger... should allow me to get a little closer to Z23.
401250.unlock: 1936-A class destroyer Z25, reporting in. Please be at ease, I shall do my utmost in battle.
401250.feeling4: Recently, I've become more and more conscious of the commander. When we are together, I simply can't seem to calm down. Mr. Anchor... what should I do...?
401250.feeling1: Mr. Anchor... I don't want to be here anymore...
401250.propose: So, you heard everything that I said to Mr. Anchor.... Ughh, I'm such an idiot! However, I'm really happy that you chose to give this to me. Th-there's no going back on this!

401250.touch2: Oooh! ...If that was on purpose, you'd better grit your teeth!
401250.mission: Don't procrastinate on your missions. Hurry up and get them taken care of!
401250.home: Good work, everyone. Let's use this time to also check the status of all the equipment.
401250.win_mvp: Not bad, let's keep this same tempo going!
401250.expedition: The commission team is already waiting at the harbor. Shall I welcome them back?
couple_encourage: Sis, let's do our best together!
401250.mail: New mail has arrived... it would be unfortunate if you glossed over something important!
401250.feeling3: Now, all my peers see me as being dedicated and responsible, and want to sortie or go on commissions with me. Commander also feels more at ease when I am around. Mr. Anchor, I've managed to make it!
401250.lose: This battle... I'll have to reflect upon it thoroughly...

301250.detail: Though I sometimes wish Yuugure would be a little more independent, thinking about that... feels a bit lonely.
301250.touch: Jeez, Yuugure, don't pull on my... Wh-what? I mistook Commander for Yuugure?
301250.login: Commander, did you sleep well? We might get a bit busy today~
301250.battle: Everyone, be on the lookout for enemy airstrikes!
301250.hp_warning: Things are getting... a little messy...
301250.feeling2: Ariake-class? Ah! There was something like that at some point but it was changed back later, not that I mind. What about Yuugure? Well...
301250.mission_complete: Come to think about it, Yuugure always has to tell me whenever she finishes a mission...
301250.main: Commander, did you know that Shiratsuyu and Shigure technically are my sisters, considering that they were Ariake-class? |Commander, if you don't develop good lifestyle habits now, it'll come back to bite you in the rear later. |Commander, want a bento? I'll make your portion along with Yuugure's this evening.
301250.feeling5: Hmm, hmm. Yeah, it might not be a bad idea to become Commander's little sister. What do you think? My domestic skills are of the charts, you know?
301250.unlock: I'm Ariake of the Hatsuharu class. Commander, pleased to meet you... Ah right, I just remembered! Is Yuugure posted here? If so, she hasn't been causing any trouble for you, has she?
301250.feeling4: Having taken care of Yuugure, Shiratsuyu, and sometimes even Shigure for such a long time, I can't just flip the switch so easily and become clingy and dependent myself...
301250.feeling1: Do all commanders go through a rebellious phase?
301250.propose: See, super-domestic little sisters are in high demand right now! But... I will admit it's a little embarrassing~♪ Hehe... From now on, you can depend on me even more. I'm very confident in my skills~
301250.profile: I formed the 27th DesDiv along with Yuugure, Shiratsuyu, and Shigure. Since I was the eldest, I suppose that made me the big sister... We got along well and worked hard throughout various campaigns, but in the end, Shigure was the only one left... Well, that's war for you~
301250.touch2: Jeez, Commander, you're not a child anymore, so please have some tact.
301250.mission: Looks like we've got new missions. Any transport operations? Those are my specialty~
301250.win_mvp: MVP, huh? I'm satisifed as long as I was able to help~
301250.expedition: Commander, while you were spacing out, the commission has already finished~
couple_encourage: Hush, hush, Yuugure. The battle's about to begin.
Shigure, you look like you're up to no good again.
Shiratsuyu, follow me.
301250.mail: Commander, I left your mail in a pretty visible place, so go take a look later.
301250.feeling3: Although Yuugure is sometimes a bit clingy, that's part of what makes her cute. Hey Commander, if I was to cling to you, would you be happy?
301250.lose: I wouldn't mind resting up in the docks if not for this whole getting beat up thing...

301631.detail: I wonder if I can find Arashio here at school...?
301631.touch: Commander... do you also want Mr. Kitty to rub against you?
301631.login: It's time to go to school again... Commander, want to walk with me?
301631.main: How nice it'd be to go to school with Arashio... |Mr. Kitty always likes to rub against peoples' legs. |*yawn*...It feels nice to take a nap during class, but... I probably shouldn't, right?
301631.unlock: My name is Asashio, and I just transferred here today. Pleased to meet you... Even though I might not be able to get caught up with the course work, Mr. Kitty and I will do our best.
301631.drop_descrip: My name is Asashio, and I just transferred here today. Pleased to meet you... Even though I might not be able to get caught up with the course work, Mr. Kitty and I will do our best.

301630.detail: I'd like to stay here forever... But at this rate, I won't be able to find Arashio.
301630.touch: Don't worry, I... am not afraid anymore!
301630.login: Welcome back, Commander. If you don't want to set sail right away, why don't you rest first?
301630.battle: Anti-air preparations... is everything in place?
301630.hp_warning: The situation... seems to not be ideal.
301630.feeling2: Every time I look out into the horizon, memories of that time come flooding back to me...
301630.mission_complete: The mission rewards... can I use them to buy something to eat?
301630.main: Dampier Strait? I don't really want to think about that place anymore... More importantly, Commander, can you install another anti-air gun? |Happiness is a full belly and a good night's sleep. |*Yawns* ...It's already so late, but Commander is still at it... Please make sure to take care of yourself.
301630.feeling5: Commander, you're somehow always able to put my heart at ease. But recently, I've discovered something else that scares me... Commander, you'll always stay by my side... right?
301630.upgrade: I think... it'd be better to mount another anti-air gun.
301630.unlock: I am Asashio. I've come to join this fleet in order to search for my missing comrade. Commander, do you also have someone who you could not give up on?
301630.feeling4: Commander, I'm at ease when I'm with you... But every time I think about Arashio, I get anxious again...
301630.propose: If there's one good thing that's happened to me, it's that I was able to meet you, Commander. Will you stay by my side until I fall asleep? Tonight... and tomorrow... and every night...
301630.skill: This time... I won't fail again!
301630.profile: Asashio-class nameship, Asashio. Arashio and I, along with our friends, formed the 8th DesDiv. Though we were disbanded in the end, I strongly believe that we'll be able to be together again one day. Commander... do you want to help me find them?
301630.mission: Commander, your missions... Please show some motivation once in a while.
301630.home: There is nothing more reassuring than being here. Commander, don't you think so too?
301630.win_mvp: It seems that I accidentally did something awesome...
301630.expedition: Isn't it about time to welcome the others back?
couple_encourage: This time... let's go home, together.
I also like cute girls. Hm? It's not the same?
I love to sing as well~
301630.mail: Shall I go through the email for you? Maybe there's a letter from Arashio...
301630.feeling3: I had another nightmare yesterday. Commander, would you please stay with me tonight? That black abyss, not being able to see anything... I'm scared...
301630.lose: If only I had upgraded my anti-air equipment a bit more...

101400.detail: Commander, who do you like more - Lexington, or Saratoga? Or... perhaps some other girl has caught your eye?
101400.login: Commander, welcome back. It's the start of a bright new day!
101400.battle: Everyone, let's give it our all!
101400.feeling2: Commander, you're not too busy right now, are you? Umm, I'd like to... here, I have a little bit of candy for you~♪ Some sugar is good for the brain!
101400.mission_complete: Mission complete! It's a pretty good haul isn't it, Commander~
101400.main: I had a dream that I would one day share the stage with Lexington. If I could sing and dance just like her, which one of us would you support? |*pouts* Another training exercise? You keep saying next time... I want to sortie and go on real missions with everyone else! |Dewey really looks after me. Maybe she's also one of Lexington's fans, hehe~!
101400.feeling5: Commander, what's different about me today? Have you noticed yet? ...You still haven't noticed it? Hurry, hurry, hurry up and notice it, okay?
101400.upgrade: Hmm... I don't particularly feel any different. Whatever, a gain is a gain~
101400.unlock: Greetings, my name is Aylwin. I'm actually quite talented at nautical navigation, so please allow me to be your guide.
101400.feeling4: Commander, you're the type who likes it when there's a bit more to love, right? ... I'll drink plenty of milk and eat lots of candy every day so that I can be your ideal type~
101400.feeling1: Commander, listen up. If this continues on, I'll be keeping my distance from you...
101400.propose: Commander, I don't mind if you have a thing for Lexington. But you have to swear that you absolutely love me, okay? I try my best every single day to be your ideal girl, so don't take your eyes off me, okay?
101400.drop_descrip: Farragut-class destroyer – Aylwin, Hull Number DD-355.
101400.skill: Looks like it's time for Aylwin to get serious!
101400.profile: I am Aylwin, from the Eagle Union. During the war, I carried out many operations as well as training exercises, and had some ties with both the Royal Navy and Iris Libre. I admire elegant, mature women like Lexington. Commander, I look forward to working with you!
101400.touch2: Jeez, Commander... That's a foul, you know?
101400.mission: New missions have been posted~ Let's hurry up and set sail! Just kidding, we still have plenty of time right now.
101400.home: Commander, you're finally back~! Did you bring back some some delicious treats for us? Thank you so much! I'll be helping myself~♪
101400.win_mvp: Yay, I'm the MVP! Surely a wonderful commander like you would have something nice for me, right~
101400.expedition: The military commission has been completed. Commander, why don't we head down together to welcome everyone back?
couple_encourage: Lexington, I'm always here to protect you~
Dewey, take a close look at my skills~!
101400.mail: Hm? There seems to be some new mail... Hrmm... Ah! Now, this seems like some good news!
101400.feeling3: Compared to Dewey, I'm only a tiny bit more... H-huh? I'm not chubby! Jeez, Commander, I'm not talking to you anymore!
101400.lose: Oops, guess I lost... Commander, can you give me some candy to cheer me up...?

303118.detail: I brought my katana with me in this wedding dress. It's just hiding somewhere that you cannot see.
303118.touch: Commander, please focus on the work... or are you purposely teasing me just to see my troubled face?
303118.login: Commander, come and try my cooking.
303118.battle: Will any of you be able to stop me today?
303118.mission_complete: Mission complete... I feel so happy after seeing the Commander's efforts.
303118.main: I think that each and every day we spend together is a blessing. | After today's training, I will replenish our food supply... am I... a good wife? N-nothing.|{namecode:67} said that my expressions have been softened recently, heehee, that's because now I smile whenever I think of you.
303118.feeling5: As someone who only lives for training, I'm really happy and lucky to be able to find and bond with you, Commander.
303118.unlock: Commander, I've been undertaking countless bride training sessions in order to prepare for this day. As your bride, I won't let you down.
303118.drop_descrip: Commander, I've been undertaking countless bride training sessions in order to prepare for this day. As your bride, I won't let you down.
303118.touch2: C-Commander, we are still in the office...
303118.mission: Commander, don't get sloppy during the mission.
303118.home: I'm slowly getting used to waiting for your inevitable return.
303118.mail: I just received a new mail.

401230.detail: If you have the time to stare at me, shouldn’t you go back to your studies? Even I... can get embarrassed...
401230.touch: If you’re free, why not help with some paperwork?
401230.login: There's still quite a lot to be done today. No procrastinating!
401230.battle: Let’s go! It’s time to reap the rewards of our hard work!
401230.hp_warning: I've got to find a way out of this mess...
401230.feeling2: Studying is important! A wise man once said, "knowledge is power." ... France is bacon? Jeez... just what is going through that head of yours?
401230.headtouch: I’m not the kind of girl who you can fool with just a few headpats. Get back to work, Commander.
401230.mission_complete: Commander, the mission rewards have arrived.
401230.main: Don’t worry, Commander. The fact that you care about me is enough.|I wonder if there’s something I can do for you, Commander. You seem tired lately, so maybe a massage would be good?|See, Commander? You can do it if you set your mind to it!|Huh? What am I in charge of? A-ahaha... I, uh... forgot...|Headpat? You mean like this...?
401230.feeling5: Commander, did you know that the higher you stand, the further you can see, but also the lonelier you will be? I hope that you can rise to great heights one day, but still be as happy then as you are now.
401230.upgrade: Commander, I hope that we'll improve, together!
401230.unlock:
Guten Tag, Commander.
I am Z23. Let’s study hard together and aim for the top!
401230.feeling4: Commander, why are you staring at me? You think I’m pretty when I look serious? I-idiot! Go do your own work...
401230.feeling1: Commander, can you not bother me when I’m trying to study?
401230.propose: This is the proof that Commander acknowledges me... Understood. From now on, I shall stay by your side and work hard to ensure that your life is happy and upstanding.
401230.profile: I’m Z23, the eldest sister of the 1936A-class destroyers. Unlike my sisters before me, who all had a namesake, my younger sisters and I only had a serial code for our names. It might be a little cold and impersonal, but I believe it’s also more convenient. So please, feel free to call me Z23.
401230.touch2: This isn’t something a commander should be doing...
401230.mission: Completing missions is a great way to hone your skills. Don't ever forget that!
401230.home: We still have so much to review about the previous battle...
401230.win_mvp: Battles are like exams. Earning MVP is like getting the top score on a test.
401230.expedition: It’s about time! Please put aside your work, and check on the results of your commissions.
couple_encourage: Z25, let's do our best together!
401230.mail: There’s mail for you, Commander. You sure are popular.
401230.feeling3: You’re a bit tired? Very well, getting rest is important. You want a lap pillow? I guess it’s fine... just for a little while...

301632.detail: So warm... Commander, would you like some? Here, you should enjoy hot tea like this... Fwoo, fwoo... Then just let the warmth spread over you.
301632.login: Commander, would you like some hot tea and a mikan orange?
301632.main: Are you cold, Commander? ...That's no good. Mm, you'll warm up if I give you a hug like this.|I can't finish all the food that everyone brought... Commander, if you don't mind, could you help finish mine?|Even though we can't have a tea party during the winter, it's fun to sit around and chat with everyone inside the kotatsu.
301632.unlock: Happy New Year, Commander. I am here to spend the New Year with you. Would you be so kind as to first help me down from here?
301632.drop_descrip: Happy New Year, Commander. I am here to spend the New Year with you. Would you be so kind as to first help me down from here?
301632.win_mvp: For your sake, Commander, I shall do my best.
301632.mail: There are still letters coming in even though it's New Year's day.

305141.detail: I'm not much of a drinker, but I should at least have a little bit of social sake. What will you have, Commander? I could get you something alcohol-free right away.
305141.touch: I hardly ever get the chance to put this outfit on. Aren't you glad to see me wearing it, Commander? Hahaha~
305141.login: Good morning, Commander. What do you say we take this day off and relax?
305141.headtouch: Y-you don't need to stare at me...
305141.main: You got this, Team Red! Mop the floor with those Team White clowns! ...Do you want to stay and watch TV with me, Commander? This match is definitely worth watching.|I always end up oversleeping on the day after the holiday's over... *Sigh*... Me dropping the ball when it really matters is not funny at all.|"Treasure every moment of peace you get," as someone once said. We're only simple "people", after all.
305141.unlock: Good morning, Commander. Everyone else seems to be dressed up on this day of celebration, so this shouldn't be a problem, right?
305141.drop_descrip: Good morning, Commander. Everyone else seems to be dressed up on this day of celebration, so this shouldn't be a problem, right?
305141.home: I owe my thanks to the girls who prepared this outfit for me. It'll help me get through the holidays without personally standing out. ...It'll have the opposite effect? Huh?!

207031.main: Commander, how does it taste? Today’s scones are Edinburgh’s signature dish. | Commander, black tea is supposed to be sipped~ At the very least, pay attention not to spill your drink. | Compared to the glaring sunset, I prefer this bright and gentle sunlight, what about you Commander?
207031.unlock: Sun kissed skin, scrumptious snacks and delicious black tea. It’s as if both my mind and body have been rejuvenated— Commander, care to join me for some leisurely chit-chat?
207031.drop_descrip: Sun kissed skin, scrumptious snacks and delicious black tea. It’s as if both my mind and body have been rejuvenated— Commander, care to join me for some leisurely chit-chat?
207031.touch2: Commander, you can’t act this way… at the tea party.

102150.detail: Commander, what do you do for your own training? Why don't you come join us down here every now and then?
102150.touch: How strange, Commander, you're also a fan of the "bro fist?" I thought we were the only ones who used that greeting.
102150.login: Welcome back, Commander! Today's a fine day to sortie!
102150.battle: All the stars in the sky are our enemies! Everyone, fiiiiire!
102150.hp_warning: Scars are the only battle honors I need!
102150.feeling2: Before I met you, Commander, I felt like I was always trapped within Cleveland's shadow.
102150.mission_complete: We were able to complete our mission without a hitch because of everyone's superb teamwork!
102150.main: I want to fight alongside my sisters again, just like at Augusta Bay. |I want to be able to dominate the battlefield with swagger, just like Cleveland. |Even though many of my younger sisters were converted into light aircraft carriers, I'm not jealous of them at all. After all, it's best to be yourself.
102150.feeling5: Commander, you are the one who I admire and look up to the most... so if one day, you ever decide to turn your back on the person you are now, I will make sure... to drag you back!
102150.upgrade: I'll make sure to put this power to good use!
102150.unlock: Hello! I'm Denver, 4th Cleveland-class cruiser and Knight of the sea! Before I officially start working for you, I've got one question: what is the future you want to see?
102150.feeling4: Even though I don't think I can ever truly grasp the kind of future that you are envisioning, if it is something that you can stand by firmly, it must be very dazzling and beautiful.
102150.propose: Commander, your ideals and morals are loftier and purer than anyone else's... From now on, can I have the privilege of being your sword so that I may cut aside everything barring you from your future?
102150.profile: I am Denver, fourth ship of the Cleveland-class light cruisers. I fought hard alongside my sisters in the Battle of Empress Augusta Bay. Though I still lack experience, I won't let you down, Commander!
102150.touch2: Commander, what are you trying to feel for?
102150.mission: Rain or shine, hell or high water, I'm always ready to sortie!
102150.home: Welcome back! I prepared some refreshments, but... Sorry, this isn't exactly my forte.
102150.win_mvp: Let's seize the day! And the next!
102150.expedition: Let's load up some extra supplies. In a battle of attrition, we can't let supplies run out before our spirits do.
couple_encourage: Cleve, you're always kickin' ass!
102150.feeling3: I've relentlessly honed my skills in order to defeat all our enemies, but... is that really all there is to life?

401210.detail: Is there something on my face? Stop staring at me!
401210.touch: Didn't we agree that you'd give me a heads up before poking me?
401210.login: Commander, you're back! Eh...? It's... it's not like I actually care!
401210.battle: Come on everyone, let's give it our all!
401210.feeling2: I'll fight to protect my sisters... Not you!
401210.mission_complete: I-I suppose you deserve a little bit of praise... but only for your hard work.
401210.main: You should be more careful if you want me to be your flagship... Don't misunderstand, I'm not actually worried about you.|I'm staying beside you, but only because its my duty as secretary ship!|If you're really tired, I suppose you could rest on my lap for a while...
401210.feeling5: Is there anything you'd like to tell me, Commander? Eh... nothing? I-i-idiot!
401210.upgrade: Thanks... for nothing! I didn't say anything!
401210.unlock: I am Z21, Narvik Z-class destroyer flagship, Wilheim Heidkamp! Since you worked so hard to find me, I suppose I'll have to follow you home.
401210.feeling4: I'm not following you! We just happened to be going in the same direction! Where am I going...? Why... why should I tell you?!
401210.feeling1: I'm having a bad day... Just stay away from me!
401210.propose: Since you're being so sincere, I'll... accept... reluctantly! But that doesn't... it doesn't mean that I've agreed to anything yet... Ah, alright, don't leave. Yes, I agree!
401210.skill: Combat will be no problem, as long as we put in a little effort.
401210.profile: I am Z21, Iron Blood Navy Z-class 1936-Type destroyer. I was the flagship during Operation Weserübung, but was sunk by HMS Courageous. I won't lose next time!
401210.touch2: Ah! What... what are you doing? One more time and I'll really get mad!
401210.mission: You're still not going to work? ...You prefer staying with me? You... you're doing this on purpose, aren't you?
401210.win_mvp: Well, I suppose you did contribute a little bit...
401210.expedition: Good work, everyone! Except the one who's always goofing off in port... *ahem*
401210.mail: There's mail for... help you open it? I... I guess I can do that, reluctantly of course...
401210.feeling3: What kind of stuff do I like? Why should I tell you? Well, I guess those macaroons we had yesterday were pretty good.

304042.detail: Seriously, you'll only ever find looks like this in fashion mags. It's an Eagle Union thing, according to Kongou...
304042.touch: You think it looks good on me? ... Sounds more like you're just poking fun at me for your own amusement.
304042.main: Hey, Commander, could you support me for a sec? ... Phew, it'll take some time to get used to these high heels.|A group photo? Sure thing. Hey, you suggested it, don't shy away from the camera. Okay, say "cheese!"|Need a break, Commander? All right, then let's head to Hiei's place and ask her to make us some tasty grub.
304042.unlock: Being in front of my sisters in this outfit is one thing, but it really is embarrassing to be wearing it in front of you, Commander. Um... ahem! What do you think? Since you're here, want to walk down to the beach together?
304042.drop_descrip: Being in front of my sisters in this outfit is one thing, but it really is embarrassing to be wearing it in front of you, Commander. Um... ahem! What do you think? Since you're here, want to walk down to the beach together?
304042.touch2: C-Commander, this outfit really bothers me... so could you p-p-please stop...
304042.home: Geesh, just standing around in this outfit draws a ton of attention... Maybe I should just change back into my regular clothes...

307031.touch: Commander, there are some plans for the New Year here. Would you please take a look?
307031.login: Even though it's the New Year, there is still no shortage of work left to do.
307031.main: Teaching the children how to write New Years' cards is unexpectedly fun. Just reading their innocent thoughts is enough to heal me. |Commander, I'm not some demonic taskmaster... As long as the work gets done, I don't really mind if you set some time aside to relax. |Commander, would you like to go visit the shrine with me?
307031.unlock: I tried wearing something a bit different from usual, but I'm not sure it suits me... Commander, what do you think?
307031.drop_descrip: I tried wearing something a bit different from usual, but I'm not sure it suits me... Commander, what do you think?
307031.touch2: Commander, this outfit was not tailored for the purpose of satisfying your depravity.
307031.win_mvp: That's why I've been saying... even though it's the New Year, you can't afford to take it too easy.

101421.detail: I can help everyone out and get some training in at the same time. This is the kind of work that I like.
101421.touch: Is there anything you'd like me to deliver?
101421.login: Let's use this jack-o-lantern to decorate your office. I'm putting it right here.
101421.main: Rumors of wasabi-flavored candy? Never heard of it. I'm just the delivery witch. |Ghosts and monsters? If they exist, line 'em up and I'll knock 'em down. |My broom? Who needs to fly when you can just run faster.
101421.unlock: I am the courier of the night. In other words, it's my job to bring stuff straight to you, Commander. Here you go, this jack-o-lantern is for you.
101421.drop_descrip: I am the courier of the night. In other words, it's my job to bring stuff straight to you, Commander. Here you go, this jack-o-lantern is for you.
101421.home: Candy? Forget it, eating too much of that junk will just erase all your gains... Fine, just one...

206040.detail: My... appearance? Right, well, my name derives from a mythological creature, so that's why I look rather... fantastical?
206040.touch: You want to try pulling my bowstring? Hehe, it's harder than it looks, huh?
206040.login: Commander, I swear to follow the examples of my Elders and strive for greatness once more today!
206040.battle: Elders, let us strive together for victory!
206040.hp_warning: Just as the Elders do, I shall hold fast!
206040.feeling2: Commander, would you mind introducing me to some of the fleet Elders? I don't much like being alone...
206040.mission_complete: Commander, how should we handle the mission rewards?
206040.main: By the way, supposing I really was a "Centaur," like a half-man, half-horse? Wouldn't that be funny...? What do you think, Commander?|Peaceful, carefree days certainly are lovely, and yet I can't help but wonder from time to time, why was I even born?|Serving as your secretary ship gives me so many chances to interact with the Elders. I can learn so much from them. Thank you, Commander!
206040.feeling5: I understand now that the others are ordinary people, just like me. But it's still not wrong to treat them with respect. ...Not only as their Childe, but also as their sister-in-arms.
206040.upgrade: Thank you, Commander. I continue to strive toward the examples of my Elders.
206040.unlock: So this is the place where all my Elders who fought in the Second Great War gather... Greetings, Commander, I am Centaur, at your service.
206040.feeling4: Spending so much time with the Commander and my Elders has shown me a side of you I never expected to see. For example... Admirable person though you are, Commander, you do sneak away from your duties from time to time. Hehehe.
206040.feeling1: How could my beloved fleet turn out like this...
206040.propose: Having been born into a world of peace, I certainly can't say I am glad to fight... But to meet you, Commander, and to be assigned to your fleet, these are the things that truly make me glad.
206040.skill: I've learnt from the Elders, I'll show you their courage!
206040.profile: I am called Centaur, name ship of the Centaur-class aircraft carriers. As I was constructed only after the Second Great War, I lived a peaceful life, in spite of it all. And so to me, all the ships of the fleet, even the little destroyer girls, are my Elders. I am at your disposal.
206040.mission: Commander, shouldn't you head out to complete this mission? I'll accompany you.
206040.home: I'm learning a lot from how you and the Elders fight, Commander.
206040.win_mvp: Commander, I think I'm catching up to the Elders, maybe, just a bit...?
206040.expedition: I can hear it. A whisper on the wind... Hehe, just kidding. Huh? The commission team has returned.
couple_encourage: Elder One, it is an honour to fight by your side!
206040.mail: Commander, some new mail has come in. I'll go fetch it for you.
206040.feeling3: It, it isn't really that shocking that I use polite language with the destroyer Elders... is it? B- but to me, those girls are also my Elders, worthy of respect!

10700060.detail: Are you that curious about me? Well, you'll have to beat me in a game first~
10700060.touch: What's that? You're going to play with me? What a boss!
10700060.login: Still asleep~? Nihihi~ Practically begging to be pranked...
10700060.battle: Who's next on the chopping block~?
10700060.hp_warning: The legend of Ami Futami has only just begun!
10700060.feeling2: Oh, Commander! Have you seen Mami around? Hmm. We had promised to play games together though...
10700060.headtouch: You planning on pranking me?...Interesting, bring it on~!
10700060.mission_complete: Mission complete~! Don't you think I worked pretty hard too?
10700060.main: There are so many people at the port~! I wonder who I should prank next~♪|Yay!!! I pulled an SSR!!! I feel crazy lucky today~☆|Hey hey, Commander~ ...Hmm? What am I going to be doing with this broom? Fufufu~ That's a secret, of course♪
10700060.feeling5: Nihihi~ Who do you think this is! ...Eh, Ami? You're correct~! As expected of the Commander! As a prize, I'll share some of my sweets with you~
10700060.unlock: Nihihi! I'm the idol, Ami Futami! This place seems awfully lively, just perfect for pranking~! See you around, Commander!
10700060.feeling4: Yeah yeah. Commander, I'm going to mimic your expression right now! ...Huh, it's not similar at all? That's strange~ When I showed my impression to everyone else, they said it was super similar~
10700060.feeling1: It's hopeless... We can't clear the stage like this, Commander~ ...Please work a bit harder, Commander~
10700060.propose: You know, showing up here, and playing with you and the others has been super fun for me~♪ I'll be relying on you to keep me entertained in the future as well, Commander!
10700060.drop_descrip: Nihihi! I'm the idol, Ami Futami! This place seems awfully lively, just perfect for pranking~! See you around, Commander!
10700060.skill: Tremble in the face of my power!
10700060.profile: The name's Ami Futami. Mami's my twin. Sometimes, I swap places with her for the day~ To tell you the truth, I might not be Ami, but actually Mami... Teehee~♪
10700060.touch2: Ohoho~ So you're that kind of person after all~?
10700060.mission: By any chance, is there still work left? If you don't hurry up and finish... Boss, the day's going to be over.
10700060.home: Good job beating'em, Commander! I'm beat, too~ Let's have a snack break~
10700060.win_mvp: Did you catch that? My shiny performance?
