10700060.expedition: Everyone did a good job returning safely! I should go and praise them!
couple_encourage: Let's make this a super epic stage together, Mami!
Harurun, don't go tripping on us now!
Iorin! Looking stylish as always~
10700060.mail: It seems like there's some new mail~ You listening, Commander~?
10700060.feeling3: Let's see... Let's put a blackboard eraser above the door to the office, and a toy rat on the chair... Woaoh! You're already back, Commander?! Tsk. Foiled again~
10700060.lose: Uh oh! My HP gauge is red!!! Retreaaat!

405023.detail: My Sakura Empire friends told me that the pine tree is like an anchor point for the gods. Much like what you are to me, Commander... Oh, just talking to myself. Hahah.
405023.touch: It feels warm... A nice change of pace.
405023.login: I waited for you, Commander. Now let us go and wish everyone a happy New Year, before aircraft come chasing after us.
405023.main: I must give my regards to my sister... But how I should face her, I do not know. Could you come with me, Commander?|Alabama proposed playing a type of badminton enjoyed around New Year's. I suppose that could be fun. ...The loser will have ink rubbed on their face? On second thought, I will pass.|I've long been used to the cold, but sometimes, I find myself reaching out towards the warmth... Commander, can I... come a little closer?
405023.unlock: They have a peculiar way of wishing a happy New Year in the Sakura Empire. In line with their traditions, I've put on this new outfit. I hope it doesn't... look strange on me. ...You like it? I see... That being the case, I'll keep wearing it for the time
405023.drop_descrip: They have a peculiar way of wishing a happy New Year in the Sakura Empire. In line with their traditions, I've put on this new outfit. I hope it doesn't... look strange on me. ...You like it? I see... That being the case, I'll keep wearing it for the time
405023.touch2: *sigh*... Could you please mind your manners in public?

207038.detail: I'll always be with you no matter where you go, Commander!
207038.touch: Just whisper in my ear if you have anything to say~! *giggles*
207038.login: Greetings, Commander. Did you have a good rest?
207038.main: When will true peace come to these waters?|Commander, my heart is beating so fast. Can you feel it?|You're always number one in my heart, Commander.
207038.unlock: The end of sorrow, the beginning of happiness, and the desire for eternity.
207038.drop_descrip: The end of sorrow, the beginning of happiness, and the desire for eternity.
207038.touch2: I'm not opposed to intimacy, every now and then~!
207038.home: Tired, Commander? Why not take a rest? Eh, on my lap? It can't be helped I guess.

199013.detail: I've got a game tournament by noon and barbecue in the evening. Having so much on my schedule makes me a happy gal!
199013.touch: Remember to keep a real tight hold on my hand, Commander!
199013.login: You wanna go for a dive too, Commander? Aight, then I'll be your buddy diver!
199013.battle: Got no choice but to resurface, I guess!
199013.main: Come on, Cheshire! Stop messing around and gimme a hand! You too, Georgia! Chop-chop!|Bremerton's a real cool gal! You should totally hit her up if you need life advice or if you run into trouble at the party!|Boy, I tell ya, I just love the beach! We gotta work extra hard so everyone can have a good time here!
199013.unlock: Supportive sorceress Seattle, comin' in hot! So, something got you down, my good pal? I'm up to talk about whatever's on your mind, but in return, you've gotta come to my party tonight!
199013.drop_descrip: Supportive sorceress Seattle, comin' in hot! So, something got you down, my good pal? I'm up to talk about whatever's on your mind, but in return, you've gotta come to my party tonight!
199013.mission: New missions are in! Maybe this is thanks to that "magic" thingy L'Opiniâtre talked about?
199013.home: Recreation is important for your well-being, but someone's still gotta watch over everyone!

307030.detail: If this data can be of some use to you...
307030.touch: Commander... please refrain from disturbing people who are working.
307030.login: Commander, your documents are ready. Please take a look when you have a moment.
307030.battle: I had hoped to avoid meaningless battles...
307030.feeling2: What is it, Commander? You want to learn how to play Hanafuda? I don't mind teaching you if you're actually interested... This is Matsu, which means pine... This is Ume, which means plum...
307030.mission_complete: Here is the mission reward list. Please double-check that you have received everything.
307030.main: Commander, why are you daydreaming? Please, get to work!|Take your missions seriously! Don't get distracted so easily.|All air units, lock onto the Commander and get ready to unleash your bombs!
307030.feeling5: We started with Hanafuda, and shall continue with Hanafuda. If you win the next round, I shall do anything you ask.
307030.upgrade: I shall repay you with my actions.
307030.unlock: My name is {namecode:93}. Commander, from now on, please request my permission in writing before doing anything weird.
307030.feeling4: I’ve lost track of time playing Hanafuda with Commander... Now that I think about it, weren’t you just using it as an excuse to approach me back then?
307030.propose: Commander, where did you sneak off to with the base’s funds this time? ... A gift for me? Don’t think you can - Eh? A-ahem... just this time, I will let you off the hook.
307030.profile: I am the first regular aircraft carrier of the Sakura Empire. As such, I served as the prototype for later carrier designs. Please... just don’t mention Midway.
307030.touch2: You...! Do you want me to cut off your hands?
307030.mission: Please complete the missions as soon as possible.
307030.home: You have a mountain of paperwork to sort through, but you should get some rest first...
307030.win_mvp: Do not make light of an elite aircraft carrier.
307030.expedition: The commission team has returned to port on time. Inspecting results.
couple_encourage: {namecode:94}, are you done warming up yet?
I can’t stay mad at you.
307030.feeling3: My past? There isn't much worth mentioning, but if you're interested, I can tell you while we play...
307030.lose: Impatience is unbecoming. We must reflect on our mistakes upon returning.

213012.detail: Terror really wanted to go to the Halloween party with me, but... I...
213012.login: The Halloween event has started. But, I'm supposed to wait here until it's my time to come out.
213012.main: Legend has it that real monsters come out on Hallow's Eve... Shall we search for them? |These festivities have diluted the ever darkness with noise and light... but it's not such a bad thing. |T-trick or treat...? Oh, right, you can have this special bewitched candy.
213012.feeling5: Forming a contract with a witch will allow one of your wishes to come true. In return, your souls will forever be bound, unable to separate from one another... Commander, tell me... what is your wish?
213012.unlock: "I am the witch of Hallow's Eve, here to guide your soul into the ever darkness"... that's what the concept of the Halloween witch is about, right?
213012.drop_descrip: "I am the witch of Hallow's Eve, here to guide your soul into the ever darkness"... that's what the concept of the Halloween witch is about, right?
213012.touch2: Commander, have you been possessed by a perverted ghost?
213012.home: I can hear the wailing of souls passing through the ever darkness... You want to know what they're saying...?

303120.detail: You shouldn't ask about a maiden's weight so casually~ *giggles*
303120.touch: Oh my~ Are you going to give me a massage?
303120.login: Welcome back! What should we do today?
303120.battle: Naughty children need to be punished~
303120.hp_warning: Looks like big sis needs to get a little serious.
303120.feeling2: If you don't express your thoughts clearly, Commander, nobody will ever understand you.
303120.mission_complete: Mission complete! I wonder what rewards we will get~?
303120.main: It seems like... my shoulders are always sore...|Commander~ I can see you ogling me in a daze, you know?|Hup! A little bug got into the room. You didn't see it? I'm confident in my good eyesight.
303120.feeling5: It's no good... I can't control myself anymore! Commander, won't you become mine? You don't have to worry about anything... All you have to do is listen to me, and I'll satisfy all your needs...
303120.upgrade: My whole body feels... hot... Commander, can you stay with me for a bit?
303120.unlock: Oh my, what a cute commander! Please allow your big sister {namecode:67} to take good care of you from now on!
303120.feeling4: It's all your fault, Commander... If you make such a cute face, I won't be able to keep my hands off of you...
303120.feeling1: You've been naughty, Commander. Do you want to be punished so badly? *giggles*
303120.propose: Oh my, you've caught me, Commander. Or should I say, I've finally caught you? Hehe~ I'll never let you go now!
303120.drop_descrip: Second ship of the {namecode:66}-class heavy cruisers, {namecode:67}.
303120.skill: Oh my, how should I torment you today?
303120.profile: I'm {namecode:67}, the second ship of the {namecode:66}-class heavy cruisers and flagship of the Second Fleet. Many of my sisters have followed my banner into battle. No matter the mission, just leave everything to big sister here~!
303120.touch2: You can touch me even more if you'd like... but there's no saying what might happen next... *giggles*
303120.mission: Missions have been updated. Don't forget to take a look!
303120.home: Welcome back, Commander. Are you tired? Come bury yourself in big sister's bosom~!
303120.win_mvp: Combat operations... complete! It's all thanks to your leadership, Commander!
303120.expedition: The commission fleet is back! Let's go give them a warm welcome.
303120.mail: Ara~ new mail? I wonder who it's from.
303120.feeling3: Commander, would you like me to clean your ears? Come on, don't be shy. Just leave it to me~
303120.lose: Oh my... this is a bit troublesome...

302059.detail: Commander, you've always been so kind to me~ Thank you~
302059.touch: Commander, did I become a bit more dependable?
302059.login: Gyah?! ...Commander, are you trying to scare me on purpose?!
302059.battle: Leave the anti-air support to me!
302059.main: Y-you saw something weird?! Wh-wh-where?! ...Jeez! Don't scare me like that! |Nagara said that I looked cuter before, but I think that's just because she likes to dote on me...!|Kinu seems like the dependable type, but she sometimes gives off really scary vibes... Ugh, I just don't understand her.
302059.unlock: Retrofit complete! ...Umm, Commander? ...Wh-what's the matter? Do I really look that different...?!
302059.drop_descrip: Retrofit complete! ...Umm, Commander? ...Wh-what's the matter? Do I really look that different...?!
302059.home: Welcome back, Commander! I used to cuddle up to you after you got back from a sortie? D-did something like that happen? I think my memory's a bit fuzzy~ Aha...haha...
302059.expedition: The girls in the commission fleet have come back. Hopefully they didn't bring anything weird back with them?

105121.detail: "Do I wear this all the time"? Maybe, maybe not. I'll leave the answer up to your imagination.
105121.login: Welcome back, dear! Is there anything you need a hand with?
105121.headtouch: It's true – you need the ears, or you can't call yourself a bunny girl. Hehehe~
105121.main: Whew. This feels so liberating! ...And not in any indecent sense, or anything.|Did Washington manage a proper smile today? She's got features as sharp as a knife, so it's easy to misinterpret her expression.|I am genuinely interested in bunny girl things, but it's quite awkward to actually tell people about them...
105121.feeling5: Commander? Oh, umm, this is just, err, equipment changing practice... Also, I recall you saying you like bunny girls. You still do, right?
105121.unlock: Commander? Oh, umm, this is just, err, equipment changing practice... Also, I recall you saying you like bunny girls. You still do, right?
105121.drop_descrip: Commander? Oh, umm, this is just, err, equipment changing practice... Also, I recall you saying you like bunny girls. You still do, right?
105121.touch2: I'll take that to mean you really like this outfit, am I right? Hehehe~
105121.home: Could you help out with my ribbon? It's a bit too close for my liking... Ah, thank you.
105121.win_mvp: Victory isn't the result of individuality. It's the result of good teamwork. Hehehe~
105121.expedition: Maybe I should keep this outfit on and give the commission team a real surprise when they return... Hehehe~ I'm just joking.

107039.detail: A signature victory pose and catch phrase are essential parts of a magical girl's arsenal! Commander, help me come up with something~♪
107039.touch: Commander, my wand would probably feel great when used like a baseball bat or a crowbar... Wanna let me try~?
107039.login: Whoosh! Commander, what do you think of Sister Sara's welcoming flight formation?
107039.main: Commander, how about we make all the younger Eagle Union carriers into magical girls as well~? Hehehe~ |It's time for Magical Sister Saratoga's invincible catch phrase - even if you can't see the light, it'll definitely be all right! ...Opinions? |There's nothing better than sharing Sister Sara's smiles and energy with the world!
107039.unlock: Sister Sara is leaving her nest and going in a new direction! I'm now making my official debut as Saratoga: The Little Witch Idol! I'm leaving my PR to you, Commander~
107039.drop_descrip: Sister Sara is leaving her nest and going in a new direction! I'm now making my official debut as Saratoga: The Little Witch Idol! I'm leaving my PR to you, Commander~
107039.touch2: Aww, Sister Sara's not fit to be a bride anymore~
107039.home: Welcome back~ Feel free to hang your coat on my planes or something~♪
107039.win_mvp: Please vote for your cute li'l Sister Sara! Thank you~♡

605051.detail: It's always the normally quiet types that end up making the boldest statements at the beach...
605051.login: Curses... I can't believe people are seeing me in this soggy, ugly mess... What, I'm cute? Wh-what kind of sick joke is that? Come help me already!
605051.main: Huh?! Where'd that sneak attack come from? I've gotta answer back...!|Cesare, this is the only time we'll be fighting on the same front. Let's do this!|Not as much as a damn molehill on this beach... Where's a soldier supposed to hide herself...?
605051.unlock: Commander, take this. Good, for the time being, you are a now a disciple under my command. It is time for us to mete out punishment to the unruly.
605051.drop_descrip: Commander, take this. Good, for the time being, you are a now a disciple under my command. It is time for us to mete out punishment to the unruly.
605051.touch: You've helped me a lot. Thank you.
605051.home: My "ammo" is about to run out... Commander, fetch me more water!

302130.detail: For the next operation, we need to allocate resources, and... Yes? Ah, help yourself, Commander.
302130.touch: What's the matter? I'm just thinking about how to manage the fleet.
302130.login: Commander, how you spend your time off-duty is no business of mine. Once you arrive, however, please do your work properly.
302130.feeling2: I was a flagship before, but now I'm just a common warrior. Please treat me the same as you would the others.
302130.mission_complete: Rewards are here... Hmm? Don't worry. I'm just thinking about how to make our fleet more efficient.
302130.main: If being cautious is considered cowardice, then shouldn't being brave also be considered recklessness?|There is no single solution for everything. Only through comparison, practice, and even failure, can one find their own correct answer.|Even if others don't understand my actions, I'll always do what I think is right... Even if you don't understand, Commander.
302130.feeling5: Real leaders will always stick to their guns, no matter who opposes them. You can tell if their methods are correct by seeing who is willing to follow them. For example... me...
302130.upgrade: Should we consider advancing deeper into enemy territory?
302130.unlock: The battlefield can change at any second. Think rationally and act cautiously so that you may never be defeated in battle. Commander, have you been able to achieve this? Flagship of the Second Torpedo Squadron, Jintsuu, reporting for duty.
302130.feeling4: Commander, why do you think those famous generals of the past were willing to bow to their superiors? Was it the limit of their abilities, or was it devotion to their leaders? In my case, perhaps a bit of both.
302130.feeling1: You might as well just leave the fleet management to me.
302130.propose: Deciding on the best course of action before acting cautiously has always been my creed. I can now say with confidence that choosing you, Commander, was the correct decision.
302130.skill: I've been waiting for this moment!
302130.profile: I'm Sendaii-class ship No. 2, Flagship of the Second Torpedo Squadron, Jintsuu. People have criticized me for being a coward, but I proved myself in the Battle of Kolombangara. Let me show you the glory of the Second Torpedo Squadron once more.
302130.touch2: You've got more guts than I expected, Commander. Do you have the heart to face the consequences, though?
302130.mission: Your new missions have been sorted. Please take a look.
302130.home: Books cannot teach you everything. Some things can only be picked up through live combat. What do you think, Commander?
302130.mail: Commander! It's important to respond to messages promptly!
302130.feeling3: Commander, it's okay to respect my opinions, but please have confidence in your own judgment. I wouldn't be standing by your side if I didn't believe in you.
302130.lose: All ships, retreat! Do not make meaningless sacrifices.

399010.detail: Milord, w-welcome... I wasn't able to prepare much for your arrival... but would you like some tea?
399010.touch: You'd like me to put on a show? S-Sorry... in front of other people... I can't...
399010.battle: The battlefield is callous... Ibuki, advancing!
399010.hp_warning: A fight with our backs to the wall? ... Exactly what I wanted!
399010.feeling2: I would also enjoy a life of sitting atop the mountains, watching the clouds pass through the sky. But my current life here isn't so bad either.
399010.mission_complete: Milord, there's a big pile of stuff over there... Um, are those the rewards then?
399010.main: Spending time alone with Milord... somehow... makes my heart pound... |Milord, if you have no further orders for me, may I go over there to meditate? |In order to hone my swordsmanship, I practice my strokes a thousand times every day... Don't worry, Milord, I already finished while you were gone.
399010.feeling5: The mugwort on Mount Ibuki is said to symbolize love that burns quietly... F-For example, right now, Milord... can you feel Ibuki's heart?
399010.upgrade: Is this... the sensation of getting stronger? Thank you!
399010.unlock: Was it your voice that beckoned me from my timeless slumber? This lowly Ibuki, though still in training, shall be yours to use as you see fit.
399010.feeling4: After spending a lot of time with everyone else, I've experienced firsthand how difficult it can be to express my emotions clearly... such as joy... and love...
399010.feeling1: Had I known I would have to serve a person like you, I never would have manifested during this era...
399010.propose: I never knew that having my feelings be reciprocated could be so overwhelmingly joyful... Milord, p-please don't look at me... I'm so happy that... my face must look strange...
399010.skill: The pinnacle of Ibuki... resides in this single strike!
399010.profile: Milord, are you interested in me...? Mm... this Ibuki, who was never born, and has no history or accomplishments to speak of... Um, my hobby is poetry, and I'm skilled in swordsmanship! Are you satisfied with that? Um, also, I'm not very good around people...
399010.touch2: Clear the mind, and purify the six roots... Eek! Mi, Milord...
399010.mission: We seem to have new missions. Would you like Ibuki to accompany you?
399010.home: Milord, if you are ever injured, please allow Ibuki to treat you with this mugwort liniment. There's still a lot left.
399010.win_mvp: My skills are but party tricks, unworthy of such praise.
399010.expedition: Milord, the comm... Um, whatever these are called. Yes, they're done now.
399010.mail: Milord, your mail... Huh? You'd like me to read it? B-but that's embarrassing...
399010.feeling3: I'm cool, you say...? If anything, I am somewhat jealous of how everyone can always have a smile on their faces... In contrast, I simply do not know how to express my emotions...
399010.lose: Ugh... I must increase my training multifold.

303115.detail: I will give my all to fulfill any task I've been assigned... B-but, Commander, could you not stare at me so much? It's a bit... embarrassing...
303115.touch: I should change my pose to make it easier to take pictures? V-very well... Ugh... Th-this is too embarrassing after all...!
303115.login: Sitting in this same pose is rather tiring, but this is also part of my training. After all, improving my flexibility should not be something that goes to waste...
303115.main: The flashes from the camera are a bit too bright, but worry not about me. Commander, I shall face down each and every challenge before me. |I should try to maintain my smile at times like these? If you say so... then I shall do as you advised to the utmost of my ability. |Commander, would you mind holding onto my parasol for a bit? I need to fix my hair accessory...
303115.unlock: Ugh... S-such shameless attire... If not for Atago saying that it would benefit me to experience different things...! It looks good on me?! I, I see...
303115.drop_descrip: Ugh... S-such shameless attire... If not for Atago saying that it would benefit me to experience different things...! It looks good on me?! I, I see...
303115.touch2: I, I'm still working right now...!
303115.home: F-finally, you're back... With so many people staring at me, I was so hoping that you'd come back soon...
303115.win_mvp: Calm your spirit and dedicate yourself to the task... I want to believe that this is part of my training!

105191.detail: Tell me what you think when you're done looking. Else I'm not letting you leave.
105191.touch: I shouldn't lift this flap? Why not?
105191.login: My... plans for the party? We could go listen to Dakota play the piano.
105191.mission_complete: Oh, rewards have come in. Good stuff.
105191.main: Where's Jean Bart gone? I wanted to show her how I look.|Seems everyone's enjoying the party. Hope Dakota and Alabama are too. Me? I'm having tons of fun.|You want something, Commander? I'm gonna go get a drink. I could get one for you too if you want.
105191.unlock: Hey... Is this outfit that strange to you? Thought it looks just like what my sister's wearing... so what are you staring at? I don't get you at all...
105191.drop_descrip: Hey... Is this outfit that strange to you? Thought it looks just like what my sister's wearing... so what are you staring at? I don't get you at all...
105191.touch2: Are you getting more weird thoughts because of my outfit?
105191.home: Makeup is tricky stuff... I don't know how everyone else does it.
105191.win_mvp: Fighting while trying not to get my dress dirty... Kinda fun.

901011.detail: This is no simple inner tube, Commander. It also doubles as "ammunition storage" for my water gun! How 'bout it? Wanna taste my waterpower~?
901011.login: Commander, summer is finally here, so why such a long face~? Let's enjoy some fun in the sun on the beach~♪
901011.main: Commander, wanna share a watermelon? |Just because it's hot doesn't mean you should stay cooped up underneath the air conditioner all day. Let's play outside~!|Commander, you should also get a tan! That way, we'll match~♪ Ehehe~!
901011.unlock: It's summer~! Summer is here, Commander! Let's head down to the beach to play! I'll show you why I'm feared in water gun fights!
901011.drop_descrip: It's summer~! Summer is here, Commander! Let's head down to the beach to play! I'll show you why I'm feared in water gun fights!
901011.touch2: C-Commander... that place doesn't need any sunscreen...
901011.home: Ehehe, Commander, are you done with work for the day? Let's get going then! ...Huh? Where to? The beach, of course!
901011.win_mvp: If you underestimate me just because I'm lightly equipped, I'll gladly teach you a lesson~!

213020.detail: Your eyes look just like those weirdo' eyes, Commander...
213020.login: Commander... I've been wanting to talk... to you... about...
213020.feeling2: Aren't you afraid of me, Commander? My body feels cold... I am always depressed... I always feel.... like a corpse.
213020.mission_complete: *coo, coo*~! Commander, I've got your rewards...
213020.main: Commander, could you put away those peas? And the lawnmower……|Is is that weird for me to have a 'heart'?|Commander……are you……a wind player?
213020.feeling5: Commander... please touch my heart... It has never beaten this fast... it has never been this hot... This is all... because of you, Commander...
213020.upgrade: I feel as if my body... is much more agile now.
213020.unlock: Monitor ship... Terror... Abercrombie-class ships are no match for me and my sister... We spent a lot of time in the Dardanelles strait. Bombardment missions... piece of cake.
213020.feeling4: It's warm next to my sister, it's warm next to the Commander too... I feel like I just got a new family member... I'm so happy...
213020.feeling1: Terror is terrified of you, Commander.
213020.propose: Times like these, should I laugh, or should I cry? I'm... I'm not really sure... but Terror knows... I know I've never been this happy before...
213020.drop_descrip: Erebus-class monitor – Terror, Hull Number I03!
213020.profile:
I'm the second ship of the Erebus-class monitors.
The Abercrombie-class ships are no match for me and my sister... We spent a lot of time in the Dardanelles strait. Bombardment missions... piece of cake.
213020.mission: How about some missions for exercise...? Otherwise my knee may break again...
213020.win_mvp: Commander, I... I worked really hard. I didn't cause you any trouble, did I?
213020.expedition: Commander, commissions are finished... You know, I lost my hand during a commission. It took everyone quite some time to help me find it...
couple_encourage: Sister, I'll do my best!
Can I jump around like a monkey too?
213020.mail: A letter... Would anyone write a letter to me?
213020.feeling3: I remember my sister being with me, ever since the very first time I opened my eyes... She's always been there for me. She's my only family...
213020.lose: *Cries*... I'll try to hold out until you tow me back to port, Commander...

312011.detail: Commander, you've come to buy something, nya?!
312011.touch: *yawns* ... Commander, stop moving around so much... I'm still sleepy, nya...
312011.login: I have to work hard today as well to sell as much equipment as I can, nya!
312011.main: Uugh... the equipment isn't selling... Commander, buy it all, nya... just buy a little bit, nya... |nil|Happy New Year! Want to buy something from Akashi's store?
312011.unlock: Commander, how does Akashi's new outfit look, nya? Isn't it cute? If you like it, then put a ring on it. I mean, everyone's gone out to play... if you don't help empty my inventory, I'll go broke, nya!
312011.drop_descrip: Commander, how does Akashi's new outfit look, nya? Isn't it cute? If you like it, then put a ring on it. I mean, everyone's gone out to play... if you don't help empty my inventory, I'll go broke, nya!
312011.touch2: Nya?! Akashi is not for sale, nya!
312011.home: Commander, are there problems with anybody's equipment? Do you need replacements, nya?

905030.detail: Information request: what is Master's favorite song?
905030.login: To do: vocals, dancing, band aesthetics. Requesting establishment of Gascogne's schedule for today, Master.
905030.feeling2: Gascogne has finished compiling idol data sets and has developed a new definition of an idol's capabilities. Assessment: an idol stops wars by singing. This holds strategic significance.
905030.mission_complete: Report: working as an idol has improved Gascogne's capabilities.
905030.main: Concept in database detailed as "saving the world by singing" was analyzed and logically equated to Gascogne's ultimate goal.|"Emotion-packed singing can truly touch people's hearts"... Unable to infer meaning of said statement. Requesting assessment of Gascogne's singing ability.|Detecting factual conflict between promotional materials' claim of Gascogne being "inexpressive" and existence of installed emotion module.
905030.feeling5: Gascogne understands the meaning of being an idol and requests system alteration to uninhibit emotions. "I am counting on you, Master."
905030.upgrade: Action has no observable beneficial effect on idol abilities.
905030.unlock: Gascogne module change process complete. New directive: sing for the world. Master's order is my will.
905030.feeling4: Idol career evaluated as holding strategic significance. Requesting permission to proceed with idol work after today's operations have been completed.
905030.feeling1: Master evaluated as unbeneficial to the improvement of Gascogne's idol talents. Activating autonomous learning module. Please step away from Gascogne.
905030.propose: Being an idol means to have hope for tomorrow, an unfading smile, vigor, and passion. Now I see how much fun can be had beyond the battlefield... Thank you so much, Master.
905030.drop_descrip: Gascogne module change process complete. New directive: sing for the world. Master's order is my will.
905030.profile: Gascogne has received an alternate functionality mode and undergone minor rigging upgrades to allow for singing in combat. Numerous incorrect parametric values caused by current mode have been detected. Referring to Gascogne's default form for basic information is advised.
905030.touch2: Warning: unsolicited physical contact with idols is unnecessary. Likelihood of others interpreting said contact as sexual harassment is high.
905030.mission: Requesting approval for Gascogne's undertaking of photoshoot, performance, or radio show.
905030.home: Report: Gascogne has completed a lesson. Requesting reviewal of results.
905030.win_mvp: Assessing version protocol as effective. Gascogne will continue engaging in singing.
905030.expedition: Gascogne proposes greeting commission team with a singing performance.
905030.mail: Requesting Master's response to received invitation of competition.
905030.feeling3: Emotional activity was detected during musical performance on stage. Requesting investigation into origin of this phenomenon.
905030.lose: Gascogne requesting immediate termination of current protocol and enabling of default combat mode.

901010.detail: To be honest, I'm a little jealous of Forbin. Back then, we both weren't able to move, but she made more of the situation than me...
901010.touch: My shoulders were starting to get stiff too... Thanks a ton, Commander!
901010.login: Commander, you finally made it! What's on the training regimen today?
901010.battle: Warm-up exercises are all done! I'm setting out~!
901010.hp_warning: It's just a flesh wound! I'll tough it out!
901010.feeling2: To be an outstanding knight, it's not enough to just have the strength to protect others. You must also become wise through learning! But... I always start dozing off when I'm studying... *yawn*
901010.mission_complete: Mission complete! Huh...? I still have to tally the rewards?
901010.main: Commander, I'll teach you some stretches for those long days!|Being a commander sure is tough, isn't it? Having to micromanage this and that... My head would start spinning... |Studying just isn't my strong suit... I obviously can read all these words, but they just don't make any sense to me when put together...
901010.feeling5: Even though I still don't quite understand this stuff, there is one thing that's certain - when it comes to learning things about you, Commander, I function twice as well!
901010.upgrade: I grow stronger yet again! Thanks, Commander!
901010.unlock: Eh? Who are you... Ah! Right, you're the Commander! I'm the L'Adroit-class destroyer, Le Mars! A pleasure meetin' you!
901010.feeling4: I think I'm starting to get it, but maybe not... But, I'm so glad that you're patient enough to teach a dummy like me. Thank you, Commander!
901010.feeling1: Woah, Commander... I, I think I'll be training solo today!
901010.propose: Um... I haven't learned what I'm supposed to do at a place like this yet... Ah, um! In any case, p-please continue to take good care of me in the future!
901010.profile: Back then, I wasn't able to fulfill my duties, but... Commander, this time, I'll show you what I'm capable of!
901010.touch2: Th-this place also needs a massage? Um... it feels a little strange...
901010.mission: We're not done with the missions quite yet. Let me handle the errands!
901010.home: Commander, you've gotta sweat to burn off fat!
901010.win_mvp: I'm in first place...? Très bien! Ehehe~!
901010.expedition: Everyone's back! I'm gonna run down to greet them! Be right back!
couple_encourage: Forbin, shall I take the lead?
901010.mail: Mail's here~! I already brought it all with me, ehehe~
901010.feeling3: Commander, you'll help me study? Yay! Thank you so much! I'll be sure to... Huuhh? Wait, I have to memorize all this?! S-sorry, I have a stomachache!

303114.detail: A balanced school life is a part of the responsibilites here. Surely, I will develop valuable and translatable skills through the process of going to school.
303114.touch: This Woofy strap here? Atago gave it to me and said it'd help me look less uptight. Jeez, I'm not uptight at all...
303114.login: Woah! C-Commander? When did you get here? I-I'm sorry, I'm still not ready yet...
303114.battle: I'll show you why they call me the "School's Strongest!"
303114.main: Commander, even if you're at school, you can't slack off too much! |What clubs am I interested in joining... I wonder if there's a kendo club... |This uniform was supposed to fit, so why is it so tight... C-Commander?! What are you staring at!?
303114.unlock: Hmm... school life, huh? It's a fairly fresh experience for me. Would it be fine to pin my hair up like this? What do you think, Commander?
303114.drop_descrip: Hmm... school life, huh? It's a fairly fresh experience for me. Would it be fine to pin my hair up like this? What do you think, Commander?
303114.win_mvp: Phew... I suppose that's a good warm up.

307032.detail: I may be in the Morals Committee, but that doesn't mean I want to become a fusspot.
307032.touch: I've been talking to Hiryuu less, yet her mood hasn't improved at all... S-she's not going to run away from home, is she?!
307032.login: I think Hiryuu is in her rebellious age... She won't wear the clothes I picked out for her, and she won't walk to school with me... As her sister, it's making me feel a little bummed out.
307032.main: Please don't joke like that. My disciplined, respectful, dependable, good-mannered, and very well-raised little sister would never end up as a dirty delinquent!|Hiryuu's in her rebellious age... *Sigh*... Perhaps it's best to leave her alone for a while...|I have my planes monitoring every nook and cranny of the school. I recommend you don't do anything that would oppose school conduct.
307032.unlock: I am Souryuu of the Morals Committee. Our goal is to maintain public decency, increase student motivation, and... *Ahem*! Anyway, please allow me to oversee the school's moral codes!
307032.drop_descrip: I am Souryuu of the Morals Committee. Our goal is to maintain public decency, increase student motivation, and... *Ahem*! Anyway, please allow me to oversee the school's moral codes!
307032.touch2: All planes, prepare for takeoff! No, wait, prepare to strike!
307032.expedition: She welcomed back the commission team, just like always... She is at the point of her life where she wants to spread her wings and be free...

301130.detail: Commander, what are you looking at? Hm? Come on, tell me...
301130.touch: *Yawn*... I get so tired when people touch me...
301130.login: Huh? So this is where you were, Commander... *Giggles*
301130.battle: L-l-l-look out, get out of the way! My breaks aren't working!
301130.feeling2: Huh? Commander? Thank goodness~ I thought I'd gotten lost again... You saw me leave and come back here 5 times? *Giggles* Then today's a surprisingly lucky day~
301130.mission_complete: Commander, I brought... Huh, what's this in my hand?
301130.main: Commander, did you see my torpedo? ... It went off somewhere suddenly.|Weird... lately I seem to forget what I'm forgetting... What am I gonna do...|*Yawn*... So tired... I hope the commander isn't looking... so I'll sleep for a bit longer...
301130.feeling5: Commander, recently whenever I see you I've wanted to tell you something, and I try to catch up to you, but then I forget what I wanted to say... It has to be something important... But what could it be...
301130.upgrade: Huh... Commander, where are we? My body feels so warm...
301130.unlock: Um, I'm {namecode:15}, the first ship of the {namecode:15}-class... Hello, Commander. My name is {namecode:15}... Huh? I just said that? Hm... I don't know how to get back home, so I guess I'll stay here. I hope I can be of service.
301130.feeling4: *Whimper*... Commander, you're being mean... I thought I'd do something to you in return~ So I'll let you hug me...
301130.feeling1: Huh...? I got lost and ended up next to the commander... I'd better run...
301130.propose: Ah! Now I remember what I wanted to say! But... you said it first... even though I wanted to be the first to say it...
301130.skill: Huh? Where are we? Oh no, it's the enemy!
301130.profile: I'm the first ship of the {namecode:15}-class, but I was meant to be part of the {namecode:30}-class... Anyway, where am I? Why am I introducing myself...? I don't really know... But I hope I can be of service.
301130.touch2: Whua... it feels weird when you touch me like that...
301130.mission: We've got a job to do! This time I won't forget!
301130.home: Commander, you didn't get lost out there? Wooow!
301130.win_mvp: All ships, open fire! Wa... wait... we've already won?
301130.expedition: Commander, while I was lost just earlier, I ran into some girls who'd just completed a commission...
301130.feeling3: Huh...? Commander? I realized a while back that I'm always by your side, did you cast some kind of magic on me?
301130.lose: Gah... ow ow... what in the world hit me...?

401351.drop_descrip: Commander, and all my fellow friends of the fleet, Happy New Year's! This time, your favorite idol Z35 will be presenting a brand new Sakura-themed collaboration, "Projekt Kirschblüte!" Everyone, thank you for your continued support!

301261.detail: Commander, Belfast taught me a lot about being a maid! ... But if Ariake saw me now, she'd probably be... shocked.
301261.touch: Phew... I'm done sorting the resources... Now for the next task...
301261.login: Welcome back, Commander. I've left your juice over here. As for the resources... I'm still sorting them... I'm sorry...
301261.main: Edinburgh taught me a lot as well... She seemed to make a number of mistakes, but I still appreciate her kindness!|nil|As soon as Mikasa saw me, she yelled "Scandalous! Taisho-era servitors would never wear skirts this frilly!"... Even though I wasn't born in the Taisho-era...
301261.feeling5: A maid's job is to provide service and relieve people. ... Commander, do you find my service to be relieving?
301261.unlock: "I, Yuugure the maid, shall dedicate myself to Ariake, my sister, and you, Commander!"... Eek?! M-my skirt...!
301261.drop_descrip: "I, Yuugure the maid, shall dedicate myself to Ariake, my sister, and you, Commander!"... Eek?! M-my skirt...!
301261.touch2: ... Commander, please don't do such things to me!
301261.home: Welcome back. I was going to hide my tail and ears, but Shoukaku told me I look cuter this way... B-but saying "meow, meow~" is too embarrassing for me...
301261.win_mvp: "T-this glorious victory i-is in my Master's name!" ... *Whimper*... I can't deliver lines like these...
301261.mail: I asked Maya to take a picture of me and send it to Ariake, and she did!
301261.feeling3: I baked a Royal Navy-style cake! I'm certain this time it'll be a hit!

304060.detail: Why are you staring at me? ...is my sword too heavy? I- I can take care of myself! It's none of your business!
304060.touch: Do you have anything that needs doing? I must test myself yet!
304060.login: Good da- agh! Wahh... I hit myself with my sword.
304060.battle: Hmph! I shan't lose to the likes of you!
304060.hp_warning: Hiei never leaves a job unfinished!
304060.feeling2: I can do it myself. You go do something else, Commander.
304060.mission_complete: Puff out your chest when receiving such honors!
304060.main: Make merry? I'd love to! Where are we- oh, no. Now isn't the time for such things!|My sisters went to a place called "Royal" to study aboard... abroad? Study abroad. Hmph! I bet you don't even know what abroad is!|If you keep staring at me, I'm going to hit you with this! And it's going to hurt!
304060.feeling5: What did you think of my party, Commander? Did you have fun? Hehe, well, the next one is going to be even better, so you definitely have to come, okay?
304060.unlock: Commander? When I grow up, I’m going to serve the strongest lord in the world! Oh... but for now, I don’t mind if you help me sharpen my skills.
304060.feeling4: Can I prepare the next party? Really!? I won't let you down!
304060.feeling1: Kongou! I- I never want to see this Commander again in my life!
304060.propose: Surprised, aren't you? Hiei prepared this party just for you! After all, today is a very important day for me, because... welll... you're very important to me! There, I said it...
304060.drop_descrip: Fast Battleship, second ship of the Kongou-class Hiei.
304060.profile: Once my big sister Kongou comes back, we're going to shock the world! Until then, I need to work hard to become a leader worthy of her! But.... courtly etiquette is really hard.....
304060.mission: Completing a mission is a glorious thing.
304060.home: That was a hard-fought sortie... Now then, I didn't make any mistakes, did I?
304060.win_mvp: Such a victory goes without saying, 'tis but a trifle.
304060.expedition: Commission complete. I shall go to receive them.
couple_encourage: I feel so warm……
Kongou! Please look after me!
L- Lady Mikasa! What shall I prepare for today's party...?
Little Bunny! I won't lose to you!
304060.mail: New mail... don't tell me... it's a summons!?
304060.feeling3: Hrm... that's not right... Um.... Umm.... Commander? Can you help me with the parts I don't understand?
304060.lose: ....urk.... 'tis- 'tis but a trifle! A single defeat! Doesn't bother me at all...

207035.detail: This festival may be a foreign custom to many of us here, but I think it's delightful we get to enjoy it nonetheless. And it's all thanks to your efforts, Commander. Hehe.
207035.touch: Is there something you would like to do with me?
207035.login: How do you do, Commander? May this splendid holiday wash away all your worries.
207035.main: All these Iris flowers are not just for showy decoration, they make for some aromatherapy as well. Hehe.|These Dragon Empery decorations all have a certain... unique charm to them, don't they?|Commander, you absolutely must try the Empyreal cuisine the Royal Maids prepared. I've heard even Her Majesty praised the flavour. Hehehe.
207035.unlock: It is my honour to get to wear another faction's garments. However... this traditional Dragon Empery dress feels rather tight around the chest area...
207035.drop_descrip: It is my honour to get to wear another faction's garments. However... this traditional Dragon Empery dress feels rather tight around the chest area...
207035.touch2: Just this once, on this special day, I'll indulge your childishness~ Hehehe.
207035.home: You're looking well. What good news have you brought Illustrious today?

901012.detail: School life is all about running track under the warm sun, am I right!?
901012.login: I'll be bringing the heat at school today!
901012.main: Commander, you should get us some more phys ed classes! I mean... exercise is really important!|Listening to music is a real good way to calm your mind when you wanna relax! Let's listen together, Commander.|Huh? Forbin's heading this way with a pile of notebooks? Um, is there a good hiding place around here—
901012.unlock: Hey! Over here! Hehe. I didn't expect to run into you at school, Commander. What are you doing here?
901012.drop_descrip: Hey! Over here! Hehe. I didn't expect to run into you at school, Commander. What are you doing here?
901012.touch2: I don't need a massage right now...
901012.home: Uh oh... I can't get anything in this book to stick in my head...

213011.detail: I am still but a shadow. The only difference is, I've found a small, small thing to strive for.
213011.main: Commander, there's no need to be reserved. I still have a lot of chocolate. |nil|Commander, just being able to watch you like this, and give you chocolate, is enough to make me happy.
213011.unlock: Those who embrace the shadows will find only an illusory happiness... But for me, that much is sufficient.
213011.drop_descrip: Those who embrace the shadows will find only an illusory happiness... But for me, that much is sufficient.
213011.touch2: Were you able to touch happiness, Commander?
213011.home: Commander, would you like some sweets to replenish your energy?
213011.win_mvp: No matter how long the night, the dawn will come again...

10400011.detail: Yukatas are freakin' awesome! Even though I can't even feel the heat because I'm a hologram, I somehow feel breezier just by wearing this!
10400011.touch: If you think you can make a girl happy just by patting her head, you'd be wrong! Don't go around doing this stuff with everyone, got it?
10400011.login: Jeez, Commander~! This isn't just "sorry I'm late" levels of tardiness anymore! If you showed up any later, I would've just left without you! Fine, let's head to the festival right away!
10400011.battle: The fireworks are just getting started! TA~ MAYA~!!
10400011.hp_warning: My yukata got all messed up!?
10400011.mission_complete: Mission complete! Let's take these funds over to the festival and have a blast~!
10400011.main: Ahhh~ those candied apples look so good! But, I don't think I'm able to eat... Huh? Wait, if I'm here, then maybe... Ah- Yuudachi-chan already ate them all!? |If I'm already wearing a Sakura-style outfit, I also should match it with a set of animal ears! Benson-chan, lend me yoooours~! |I have to admit though, it's really hard to move around in a yukata... That's right! Prinz-chan, teach me the secret to fighting in this outfit~!
10400011.unlock: The clothes from the Sakura Empire are so stylish! Commander, since it's a rare occasion, let's go take a look around! Ah, of course, don't forget to run the reel~♪
10400011.drop_descrip: The clothes from the Sakura Empire are so stylish! Commander, since it's a rare occasion, let's go take a look around! Ah, of course, don't forget to run the reel~♪
10400011.mission: Slowly stockpiling resources through missions is fine and all, but wouldn't it be better to open a stall at the festival and strike it rich? Let's talk it over with Akashi-chan!
10400011.home: Good work out there~! Want to head down to the Bon Festival with Izumo and the others once you catch your breath?
10400011.expedition: I'd like to spend some more time at the festival, but it's about time for the commission fleet to return. Come on, let's head back!

307062.detail: Oh, Shoukaku was also doing this job, right? Even though she's also wearing the same outfit, she gives off completely different vibes than me...
307062.touch: Hold this position a bit longer...? Mm, can't I ask for a slightly cooler pose...?
307062.login: Commander, it's fine! You don't need to worry about me! I can totally handle something like this!
307062.main: Hmm... I just can't pull the look off as well as Shoukaku... Is this the difference in our "girlish appeal?" |Is this job just to sit here for the photo ops...? I thought I'd get to drive...|Phew...! Keep it together, Zuikaku... You've gotta look your best in front of the camera!
307062.unlock: Commander, I volunteered to take this job in order to help you out, but this outfit... did it always require such a high degree of exposure...?
307062.drop_descrip: Commander, I volunteered to take this job in order to help you out, but this outfit... did it always require such a high degree of exposure...?
307062.touch2: Commander, you're not doing this kind of stuff to the other girls, are you...?
307062.home: Ugh... Having to hold this pose for so long is making my shoulders stiff...

301131.touch: Whooahhh! ... Gosh, that was too close... Thanks, Commander...
301131.main: Commander, have you seen my torpedo...? Standing on it...? Wait... Oh noooo!|nil|Are you hungry, Commander? Umm, I have a sandwich... strawberry cake, and some coffee, if you want...
301131.unlock: H-here they come... Your order, and your cutesy dutesy maid... Whoaahh! I'm sorry! Look out!
301131.drop_descrip: H-here they come... Your order, and your cutesy dutesy maid... Whoaahh! I'm sorry! Look out!

101352.detail: I've gotta come up with a sweet victory pose... It doesn't concern weaksauce like you, but you can brainstorm with me if you want!
101352.touch: Has my tennis outfit got you crazy for me~?
101352.login: Commander, come here and help me practice! If I win the championship, you'll get a special reward♪
101352.main: They said I'm a wild card... Does that mean I'm super talented?!|Hey! Wait a sec! You're throwing too fast for me to return the ball...!|You tired, Commander? Guess what, I anticipated that you would be~! Heheh, have a taste of my deluxe honey drink! This stuff will get you back in the game, no matter how drained you are!
101352.unlock: Tada! Your favorite tennis superstar, Bache, is right here! ...Hey Commander, you're supposed to cheer for me like you're one of my fans in the stands!
101352.drop_descrip: Tada! Your favorite tennis superstar, Bache, is right here! ...Hey Commander, you're supposed to cheer for me like you're one of my fans in the stands!
101352.touch2: No weaksauce commander in the world can touch me now~! Whuah?!
101352.home: I'm practicing my serves right now! Be a nice weaksauce Commander and fetch my ball!

401350.detail: Huh? Commander, why are you in my room? ...Eh?! I'm the one who got the room wrong?
401350.touch: Commander, what's the matter? Eh, I made a mistake on this document? ...Ah, it's true! Oops, sorry~
401350.login: Hallihallo~ Commander, did you dream of me last night?
401350.battle: Let's give it our all! We're the best~!
401350.feeling2: When it comes to the Iron Blood, the cool one would have to be Z1. The sexy would definitely be Eugen. As for who is the most idol-like, that would be none other than me, the dancing and singing Ms. 35!
401350.mission_complete: As expected of you, Commander! What bountiful rewards~
401350.main: Commander, look look, a bunny! Isn't it so cute? |Just before, I went to see the Lexington sisters' Konzert. You can definitely tell that they are professionals. |Commander, what kind of performance do you like? Tell me so I can go learn it~
401350.feeling5: Commander, I am only able to perform my best when I am with you. Whether it's in combat or on stage, I am always at my best. That's why I can say... I can't be without you~
401350.upgrade: Commander, you sure are a person of great insight!
401350.unlock: Commander, my fellow fleetmembers, hello~! I am the singing and dancing Z35! Pleased to meet you!
401350.feeling4: Now that I think about it... Commander, do you know what a produzent is? It's like the agent for an idol. Commander, if you have time to spare, I'd like you to become my P~
401350.feeling1: You're not the commander I was hoping for...
401350.propose: It's a promise, Commander. When I become an idol, you'll become my P, okay? Until I become the top superstar... No, even after that, always be my P~
401350.skill: I won't let you have your way~
401350.profile: The lead ship of the 1936B-class is none other than me, though there were only three of us to begin with... I carried out many artillery and minelaying operations in the Baltic Sea, but in the end, accidentally ran into our own mines along with Z36. Yes, the same as this one down here... Eh? Why is it here?!
401350.touch2: Commander, I might be playing it cool, but you've already lost my affection points.
401350.mission: Another new mission, another new challenge~
401350.home: Commander, are you tired? You should come watch my performance to help you recover!
401350.win_mvp: Großartig! Everyone did a great job!
401350.expedition: We interrupt this broadcast to bring you a special message... Commissions have returned, Commander~
401350.feeling3: Commander is a bit like the idol of the fleet. Just by being there, you bring hope to everyone. I want to become the same kind of idol!
401350.lose: Don't lose hope, everyone! We'll have another chance!

101290.detail: Commander, do you appreciate something sweet every now and then? Here, take whatever you like.
101290.login: If my hunch is right, Commander's candy should be... Huh? Hey! There's nothing here!
101290.battle: No need to thank me! Good things are meant to be shared. I'm not gonna hog all of my candy!
101290.feeling2: I feel like my famous sisters always make me seem a bit... insignificant. Oh well, I guess there's nothing wrong with that.
101290.mission_complete: This will get rid of some of the shame from Kolombangara... (Munch)
101290.main: You really can't take the Sakura Empire's destroyer squadrons lightly!|If only everyone had lifetime supplies of candy, there wouldn't ever be another war!|Commander, why don't we fire candy at the enemy instead of explosives?
101290.feeling5: I made some chocolate just for you, Commander! Will you take it?
101290.upgrade: Don't worry, my teeth are perfect!
101290.unlock: I'm Radford, a Fletcher-class destroyer. Want a lollipop, Commander?
101290.feeling4: Have you ever tried making your own candy? It's fun! Here, try some of mine!
101290.feeling1: I'm never giving you any more candy ever again!
101290.propose: Does this mean I'm the sweetest candy in the world to you, Commander? ... Okay, so... I guess that means I'll be your lollipop from now on?
101290.drop_descrip: Fletcher-class Destroyer - Radford, Hull Number DD-446!
101290.profile: I'm Radford, DD-446, part of the Fletcher-class! Hmm... and... even though I didn't do that well in the Kula Gulf and Kolombangara, I tried my best! Anyways, the only thing that matters at the end of the day is candy!

101290.mission: Now is not the time for candy... Ha! I'd never say that!
101290.home: C-Commander! Did you manage to snatch any candy from the enemies? ... They didn't have any?!

101290.expedition: Hey, Commander! How about we exchange all our commission rewards for candy instead?
101290.mail: New mail! It's not another pamphlet about how sugar is bad for your health, is it?
101290.feeling3: Hey, Commander, that candy you gave me the other day was really good. Where'd you get it?

207020.touch: Your warm hands keep me energized to keep fighting, Commander!
207020.login: Ready for orders, Commander. I am confident in any kind of battle!
207020.battle: Is that it? Hah! Swordfish squadron, prepare for battle!

207020.mission_complete: Commander, to leave your rewards unclaimed is disrespect to the mission.
207020.main: You look like you're busy, Commander. I won't bother you then. Let me know if you need anything.|Commander, umm... can you tell the destroyers to come to my room? I'd like to give them presents.|This is... So cute! *pat pat* Eh? Wh-when did you get here, Commander?!

207020.upgrade: Oh! oh! oh! Allow me to protect you, my destroyer friends!
207020.unlock: Ark Royal, reporting in for duty! I am confident in all manners of battle. Why, it was I who managed to destroy Bismarck's rudder!
207020.feeling4: G-good grief... If you were the same size as those destroyers, Commander, I wouldn't be so embarrassed... I was fine with doing this with the little ones... but with you...
207020.feeling1: You can't compare with the destroyers, Commander...
207020.propose: I'll take care of all the destroyers from now on! No one can touch Commander or my destroyers. No one!
207020.drop_descrip: Aircraft carrier – Ark Royal, Hull Number 91!
207020.skill: It's time for you to leave!
207020.profile:
Ark Royal, reporting in! I'm the first aircraft carrier specifically designed and built for the role in the Royal Navy, I'm proud of being a prototype to all other carriers that followed. 
 Little needs to be said about my feats against the Bismarck. Rather I must ask, are there any of those cute little destroyers in our fleet?
207020.touch2: Eh... Commander... please don't... Why are you doing this?!
207020.mission: Commander, it's a soldier's duty to complete missions!
207020.home: Is it time for a break? I'm going to see my destroyer sisters then!
207020.win_mvp: An enemy who loses their ability to steer will be doomed!
207020.expedition: Commissions have been completed, Commander. If there are any cute destroyers in the fleet, allow me to welcome them back myself.
couple_encourage: I feel so strong now!
I've got to set an example for the others!
207020.mail: Do you need to me read out your mail, Commander?
207020.feeling3: I thought you were finally going to have me Court Martialed, Commander! I'm grateful to finally be recognized by you. It's nothing to be ashamed of? Commander, I, Ark Royal, will follow you forever!

399050.detail: My room's a bit messy, you say? So what? There's no problem as long as I can find everything I need.
399050.touch: What is it? If you require something of me, speak your mind.
399050.login: So you've come. Color me surprised. I assumed you had overslept, but that seems to not be the case.
399050.battle: Show me the fool that dares challenge the mighty Hakuryuu!
399050.hp_warning: How could the great Hakuryuu be damaged?!
399050.feeling2: Praise me if I do well. Berate me if I do poorly. That's just how work goes. There's no need to concern yourself over me.
399050.headtouch: How dare you pat me without permission. Have you no fear of being cut down?
399050.mission_complete: See, I knew you had it in you. The ability to handle trifling chores is quite commendable.
399050.main: It is great to have access to such a wide variety of sparring opponents here... Friends? Hmph, just having one or two is sufficient.|My katana is my soul. Should it leave my side, I... Never mind, forget I said anything.|I had the opportunity to roll some rice balls during my free time. You may have them if you're hungry.
399050.feeling5: Now that you've seen my secret, I can no longer afford to let you out of my sight! Hmph, from now on, we shall do everything together! ...Of course that includes going outside to play... W-wait, this kind of feels like I'm getting taken advantage of...!
399050.upgrade: Hmph. The distance between me and the rest grows ever greater.
399050.unlock: So, this brat is supposed to be the commander? My name is Hakuryuu. Listen well – try to control me, and you will make a laughingstock of yourself. Remember this!
399050.feeling4: Umm, have you seen my katana...? I swear I left it here, but it's nowhere to be found... Ahem! A-a-anyways, if I don't find it soon, um... it's a really big deal, so please help me...!
399050.propose: You think I'd just sit there and listen to your sentimental... M-my katana?! When'd you get your hands on that?! Give it back! Please, I'll do anything you say! ...Fine, I admit defeat... Ughh, but... this somehow doesn't feel all that bad...
399050.profile: I am Hakuryuu, aircraft carrier of the Sakura Empire. Let any who dares question my might face me head-on. I shall teach them the meaning of overwhelming power.
399050.touch2: What, are you trying to imitate me? ...Hey, knock it off already!
399050.mission: Missions? I have no desire to waste my time on such trifling chores. I'll leave that to you.
399050.home: M-my katana... Phew... Ahh, I really don't feel complete without it. ...Hey, why are you still here? Do you really have the free time to stand around in a daze?
399050.win_mvp: Hmph! They sent lowly scum to try to stop the mighty Hakuryuu? How laughable!
399050.expedition: Did the commission fleet come back while I was sidetracked? Oh, you're going to go greet them? See you in a bit.
couple_encourage: Hmm, I don't think we're going to get along...
399050.mail: A new missive? ...Oh, it's not a duel challenge. Boring.
399050.feeling3: Not too bad. You might actually be able to keep pace with me... Hmph. But if you become complacent or regress, I'll cast you aside faster than anyone else.
399050.lose: L-let's get out of here! ....H-has anyone seen my katana?!

301380.mission: Commander, um... about those rewards... Huh? I have to finish the mission first?

301380.feeling3: Commander, please consort with me... Huh? That doesn't mean let's be friends?

202070.feeling5: Commander, if you don't know how to relax, just let me be your guide. Hm? What will I do? Erm, well, wait a tick and let me think! Ehehehe~

202070.feeling4: It's not like everything needs to be done one hundred percent perfectly all the time. Just take it easy. It's good enough for government work. You need to cut loose more often.
202070.feeling1: You know, Commander, if you keep pushing me like this I'm going to break.
202070.propose: Now, I know marriage is a solemn and serious ritual, but don't worry, I'm not going to stand on ceremony with you, Commander! Indeed, I have only one request: that whenever I wish to see you, Commander, you be there for me ♪
202070.profile: I am the name ship of the Southampton-class. During the war, I was the only one of my sisters to be sunk. How lucky of me... Ugh. Let's not speak of such unpleasant memories...
202070.touch2: I-I'm not a maid! ... Err, rather, you can't do that to a maid either!

202070.win_mvp: We have seized the day! Yaay!

couple_encourage: Newcastle! Might I trouble you for a spot of tea?
North and... South! Hah! I think we'll get along famously!
202070.mail: Who's the letter from this time?

202070.lose: Aieeee! L-let us beat a hasty retreat!

305142.drop_descrip: Oh. Fancy meeting you here... Walk to school together? Uh, sure! I know the way, so please just follow me.

301110.detail: If you bow deep and beg for it, I'll make your wishes basically come true! ... It didn't work? Um, well... that's because you haven't wished hard enough yet!

301110.skill: I see! This is the power that two sisters have!

301110.touch2: Uh, umm... is this what I think it is? I know full well the meaning of w-what you did! I-I see...
301110.mission: You haven't finished the mission? ... That sounds about as bad as not finishing your job.

301110.expedition: If you let a completed commission just sit there, does it gain any "interest"?
couple_encourage: Destroyer Division Six... depart!
301110.mail: I see! This is that... thingy! The thing you need to bring with you to be let into that one chocolate factory!
301110.feeling3: It's my birthday tomorrow. Have you gotten a gift for me yet? You didn't know it was my birthday? Ah, well... see that pendant over there? Buy it and give it to someone you like, I'm sure they'll be delighted!
301110.lose: I see...! Times like these you should P2GSOE2PTG4U! Pay to get someone else to play the game for you! Or you can just let me handle it instead!

301212.drop_descrip: C-Commander, I will be your partner for the party tonight. Let's see, umm... I believe this is proper Royal Navy etiquette... D-did I do it correctly?

301629.touch: Wah! This time I'll poke you in return! Poke! Poke poke~!

301629.drop_descrip: I am Tanikaze, the winds have carried me from valleys to mountaintops... Oh wow, a b-butterfly?! It really is a butterfly! Is this for me? Thank you, Commander!
301629.touch2: Ah, I see! It's my turn now! Poke poke... Scratch scratch... Can I nap while you give me a piggyback, Commander? ...Zzzzz....

107170.detail: Commander, why are you staring at me...?
107170.touch: ...Don't think I'm upset just because I have little to say. Just let me know if you need anything.
107170.login: We're in a state of emergency. Be prepared to run the Holiday Express, even if it's a holiday.
107170.battle: Why did they choose to become our enemy...?!
107170.feeling2: There is no beauty in warfare. There is only ugliness in the suffering and loss of life we inflict upon each other.
107170.mission_complete: There are a ton of rewards? Of course.

107170.feeling5: We were born as weapons of warfare, and I thought that is all we would ever be. But having spent time with you, I'm beginning to think... that there's more to our lives than war.
107170.unlock: Bunker Hill, one of the Essex-class carriers, is joining the fleet under your command. Don't worry, you'll see the extent of my abilities soon enough.
107170.feeling4: Something strange has been going on with my thoughts recently. Whenever I start thinking about things, your face pops up in my head and makes it hard for me to stay calm...
107170.feeling1: I'd rather not talk to you right now.
107170.propose: Sorry... My mind has gone completely blank... I'm lost for words... Oh, that's right! "I pledge loyalty and love to you until the end of time." ...How does that sound?
107170.drop_descrip: Essex-class aircraft carrier – Bunker Hill, Hull Number CV-17.
107170.profile: Essex-class, Bunker Hill. My name comes from a battlefield in the Revolutionary War. I've seen my fair share of battles... and know that war brings nothing but sorrow and pain. Let's not talk about it any more.
107170.touch2: By the looks of things, you won't learn your lesson without some harder-hitting "experience."
107170.mission: Missions... should best be completed in a timely manner.
107170.home: You've returned? ...Very well. Why don't we prepare for the next sortie?
107170.win_mvp: So this is the end that you all chose...
107170.expedition: Pardon, but I'll go greet the girls who are coming back from their commission. Just wait here until I report back.
couple_encourage: You are nothing before the Essex class.
Project Rainbow? ...It has a nice ring to it...
107170.mail: The mail's here... Wonder if there's any new intel?
107170.feeling3: Don't think I'm upset just because I have little to say. If anything, I'm probably thinking about something, or about how to express myself.
107170.lose: Their power... surpasses even the "Dragon's Jaws"...?

301381.drop_descrip: Huh...? Where am I...? What time is it...?

305011.drop_descrip: Yamashiro's always saying that I would look better in more trendy clothing, so she went out of her way to pick this out for me. Jeez, that girl... Oh, Commander? Does this outfit... suit me?

Take your watergun fight elsewhere! ...I'll be right back, Commander. I'm going to have a word with that wannabe commando!

605062.drop_descrip: Tired already? For goodness' sake, I thought you'd be more reliable than this. Don't go burning all your energy at once, we still have a whole day of recreation ahead of us.

301470.touch: Um, excuse me...! You're getting... a bit too touchy-feely...

301470.hp_warning: I can... hold on a bit longer...!
301470.feeling2: I don't mind feeding seagulls, or petting cute little animals... So why can I not handle being touched by the commander... *sigh*...
301470.mission_complete: Mission complete! I'm so glad that I was able to be of help to you, Commander...!
301470.main: Commander, shall I open the window? You'll feel a lot fresher if it's nice and breezy, right?|Please don't interrupt Yamakaze and Kawakaze's work... 301470.feeling5: Thanks to your help, I've become a lot better at the touchy-feely stuff... Um, if it's not too much to ask, could you continue to "practice" it with me...?
301470.upgrade: Thank you for always looking after me...!
301470.unlock: I am the revised Shiratsuyu-class destroyer, Umikaze. Commander, I hope I will be able to support you and your fleet to the fullest of my abilities... I d-do hope we'll get along!

301470.feeling1: Commander, I'm so sorry I wasn't able to help you...
301470.propose: Um, it's terribly embarrassing still, but... I finally managed to put the ring on...! Um... Commander... please allow me to stay at your side forever...!

301470.home: Commander... Ehehe, to tell the truth, I was really wondering when you would come back...
301470.win_mvp: Ehehe... It was only made possible by everyone else's hard work...

L-let's all be careful here, okay?

10100030.drop_descrip: I'm Blanc. Nice to meet you. Maybe you could introduce some intriguing books from this world to me...

10100030.win_mvp: That was great for a warm-up.

307028.detail: Your expression... exactly the same as Romeo when he lost himself in front of Juliet.

307028.login: Heh... Let's crush our foes together, shall we?

307028.unlock: To hold one's hand and grow old together with him... If it is to be with you, then it won't so bad.
307028.drop_descrip: To hold one's hand and grow old together with him... If it is to be with you, then it won't so bad.
307028.touch2: You really like to touch me here, don’t you?

701070.detail: What are you ogling me for? Are you some sort of creep?
701070.login: You've got lots of work to do. Like, that huge stack of papers on your desk.
701070.battle: I'm good on fuel. Only thing left to do is dispatch the enemy!
701070.hp_warning: I've been hurt. Mm, that's all...
701070.feeling2: I've always got my eyes on you. Mm, that's all.

701070.feeling5: All right, you're a decent person, I'll give you that. Huh? You want me to... be with you, forever? Ummmm... I-I need to think about, that's all...
701070.upgrade: Thanks for making me stronger. Yeah, that's all.

701070.feeling4: You're awfully good at putting on faces. Unless... you're actually an honest, decent person after all? I guess I'll give you the benefit of the doubt for now. Mm, that'll be all.
701070.propose: I've sailed through bad weather and finished countless tough escort missions. If I can do that, then I can promise to follow you anywhere you go, Commander. Mm, that'll be all.
701070.profile: I'm Gremyashchy, Grozny-class destroyer. I didn't just do escort missions, I squared off with enemy destroyers and rescued allies too. I've done almost everything, save for dealing with aircraft carriers, so I'm fit for pretty much any mission. Mm, that's all.
701070.touch2: Th-that confirms it, you're a creep...
701070.mission: That's a whole lot of unfinished missions...
701070.home: Here, some cookies Gromky made. As your reward for a job well done.
701070.win_mvp: That takes care of the enemies. I guess that's all.
701070.expedition: Commission team's come back. I kind of expected that you knew that already.
couple_encourage: I'll protect you.
Don't be reckless, huh... You too.
Friends...
C-can I have some of that?

701070.feeling3: You might fool Gromky, but you can't fool me. If I catch you doing anything questionable, I won't hesitate to whack you with this thing. Mm, that'll be all.
701070.lose: Ugh... That was a pretty garbage battle...

401010.touch: Don’t be so wishy-washy if you’re greeting someone.

401010.feeling2: What’s up, Commander? Are you enjoying your everyday life with me? I sure am.

401010.feeling5: Now that I think about it, the apocalypse is often associated with wild romances, or couples who cling to each other until the bitter end. Commander, why don’t we become as Adam and Eve?

401010.feeling4: Even if the world was coming to an end, I have nothing to fear. As long as you are at my side, I can continue to laugh.

401010.touch2: You want some "hard love," is that it?
401010.mission: We have a new mission. How about we take it on together?
401010.home: Nice expression you've got there. Wasn't that battle simply exhilarating?
401010.win_mvp: Hah hah hah! The great Z1 is unrivaled!
401010.expedition: A commission has been completed. Straighten up, you have to greet the hardworking girls with your best smile.
couple_encourage: Your smile is so fake.
Ha, follow me, you monkeys!
401010.mail: Hey, you have new mail. Don’t drop it!
401010.feeling3: Life is short, Commander, and I want to live life on the edge. If you are going to be my partner, you have to keep up. Now, let’s see that smile!

301390.touch: Teehee~ Commander, do you wanna find out what it takes for me to set off Peepsy's alarm?

301390.mission_complete: Wow, these rewards are "fenomennel"! ... Huh?! I'm not getting any?!

I helped Naka when she was in trouble! I think...|Commander, how do you say this word? "Try-yumf"? I dunno what that means, but I think I can do that by setting off Peepsy!

301390.touch2: Eeeep...! I knew you're a dangerous stranger! Hear Peepsy roar!
301390.mission: Commander, work harder so I can live a more "lugshurious" life!
301390.home: Hi, Commander! Where's my strawberry ice cream? Wha–? But didn't I tell you to get some?!

301390.expedition: Commissions look fun! I wanna do one too!

Ah, you don't need to consider your options at length. I picked out your present long ago, you see♪

307039.drop_descrip: If I can become stronger through this... Commander, what are you staring at? Don't you still have work to do?
307039.touch2: ... Judgment shall be exacted upon you when work is over. Prepare yourself.

301391.drop_descrip: Nagatsuki the kitty maid is at your service~ Do your best to not fall madly in love with my cute looks~! Hehe~

303140.touch: Shall we go for a stroll before the sun goes down?

303140.battle: Fleet status confirmed... prepare to open fire!

303140.feeling1: Commander, let's try to do our best?

303140.expedition: Military commission, complete. Rewards, received... Aye! I've recorded everything!

303140.feeling3: Commander, what would you like to have tonight? Um, you'd like me to decide? In that case, would you like vegetable cream stew or pork cutlets?

301350.feeling1: Ack, the Commander is here, run!
301350.propose: Wahahaha, I made it just in time, Commander?! So, so it is me, right? It must be me, right?! If it is me, then you will not be wrong by picking me, Commander!

201080.battle: A-Amazing... Does everyone fight like this??
201080.feeling2: Awww... I miss my home after all...
201080.main: Commander, why are you not giving me attention?|I'm a little homesick... Just a little!|I, er-hm! I'm everyone's idol, Comet! Should I change my pose a little?
201080.feeling5: Commander, am I shining~? Ehehe, being approved by you makes me so happy~
201080.upgrade: I am one step closer to becoming an idol!
201080.unlock: I'm Comet of the C-class destroyers! I'm happy that I have your support, Commander!
201080.feeling4: If you become my manager, Commander, I feel like I'm going to have the courage to try harder...
201080.propose: It's alright if I don't become a superstar like Ms. Lexington... Why? Because I've already got something far more valuable...
201080.drop_descrip: C-class destroyer ー Comet, Hull Number H00!
201080.skill: I wanna become the top idol!
201080.profile: I am Comet of C class. My first assignment was at the Far East, and then I got transferred to The Home Fleet to be equipped with water mine rails. Actually, I'm a little worried about rumors of something happening to the homeland...
201080.touch2: Wha! If someone see this, I won't be able to become an idol~!
201080.mission: Commander... as a manager of idols, please complete your missions properly!
201080.home: It feels good to have you around, Commander~
201080.win_mvp: Everyone, Today, I... Comet, am dazzling everyone again~
201080.expedition: Commander, the commission team has returned! ...How about I go with them next time!
201080.mail: Waa~ It's a letter from home~!
201080.feeling3: Commander, do you think a small girl like me can become an idol?
201080.lose: *cries* ...I can't grow up if I can't endure this after all...

303121.detail: Oh my, Commander... just what are you looking at~? Would you like me to bend over a bit more~?
303121.touch: The best type of swimsuit? Definitely a bikini. Don’t you agree, Commander?
303121.login: Phew... it sure is hot during the summer. Eh? Why is your face all red? Are you having heat stroke?
303121.main: Kendo sword and sunglasses... Takao, did you really come here for vacation?|Commander, you can join me under my parasol if you get too hot.|Commander, want to watch me play beach volleyball?
303121.unlock: The warm breeze that gently wraps around your skin, and delicate footsteps across the white sand... isn’t this the essence of summer? Commander, what does summer mean to you?
303121.drop_descrip: The warm breeze that gently wraps around your skin, and delicate footsteps across the white sand... isn’t this the essence of summer? Commander, what does summer mean to you?
303121.touch2: Oh my. There may only be one Earth, but Commander certainly has two hands~.
303121.expedition: Running commissions in this kind of heat is no easy feat. Let’s go properly reward our hardworking girls.

307040.touch: Be careful. You might get hurt if you get too close!
307040.battle: Victory goes the one who strikes first! Planes, take off!
307040.feeling2: Since I am always thinking about combat, the other girls keep saying that I’m not feminine at all. So, um... that’s what I’m trying to improve here.
307040.mission_complete: Your rewards, Commander. Please take a look.
307040.main: All systems go! Ready to sortie at any time.|Is it strange... that I find Souryuu’s ankle to be elegant?|Commander, if you’re bored, how about we spar?
307040.feeling5: Umm, Even though I didn't feel like anything changed.... At least the Commander has accepted to look me as a woman, When I'm by the Commander's side, I also have those girly feelings that my sis mentioned before, is that.... enough?
307040.upgrade: Hey! I’m in pretty great shape!
307040.unlock: Aircraft carrier, {namecode:94}, awaiting orders! Leave the missions to me. I’ll fight until my dying breath.
307040.feeling4: Hmm, feels like nothing has changed. But at least Commander sees me as a woman now. Whenever I’m around you, my heart skips a beat, just like Souryuu described. Is this... girly enough?
307040.feeling1: Haa! (Her fist stops next to your face) Stay away from me.
307040.propose: I’m neither gentle like the other girls nor attractive like my sister. The only thing I’m confident about is my combat prowess. Would you still be willing... to accept a girl like me?
307040.profile:
I'm {namecode:94}, a {namecode:93}-class aircraft carrier. Although I'm {namecode:93}"s sister, we're not actually the same type.
As an aircraft carrier, I simply can't afford to let my guard down during battles. Let's advance carefully, and aim for the best possible results in combat!
307040.touch2: Commander, before I smack you, I’d like to ask: Do you not see me as a woman?
307040.mission: A mission, huh? I’m looking forward to any kind of challenge.
307040.home: Here are the combat logs. Let's start reviewing the battle..
307040.win_mvp: An expected victory. It’s not even worth mentioning.
307040.expedition: Commander, your commission fleet should be back.
couple_encourage: Big sister's feet are the best in the world~!
Simply unparallaled! What an aura!
307040.mail: Mail! Eh, it’s dangerous to throw them around like airplanes? Fine...
