307040.feeling3: About acting more feminine... do you think Souryuu is more attractive because of her cold demeanor? Oh, and her ankles are amazing. It would be great if I could become like her.
307040.lose: Win some, lose some. It's only normal.

302131.detail: I said I was taking a vacation, but even out here on the beach, I'm still thinking about the affairs of the fleet... I really am a workaholic, aren't I?
302131.touch: Commander, you're concerned about it too, right? My tail is so conspicuous in this swimsuit...
302131.login: After we finish work today, how about taking a break on the beach?
302131.main: If you relax too much, you'll become undisciplined. If you're too uptight, you'll only find yourself out of breath. |Every year when it is swimsuit season, I can't help but to be envious of Sendai... Commander, I'm not being negligent in my exercise, am I? |Commander, your mind has wandered off onto the beach, hasn't it? It’s written all over your face.
302131.unlock: Hmm? Is it unusual? Hah. Even I require a change of pace to clear my mind every so often. Commander, why don't you come out and get some fresh air as well?
302131.drop_descrip: Hmm? Is it unusual? Hah. Even I require a change of pace to clear my mind every so often. Commander, why don't you come out and get some fresh air as well?
302131.touch2: You can't concentrate on your work when I'm wearing a swimsuit, right? Hehe, just consider this a test of will then.
302131.home: Here, iced coconut water. Please have some.

101090.detail: I can move quickly, so I probably won't get hit. Well... even if I do, I'll... probably be fine.
101090.touch: My little sisters would probably like doing this too. Huh? Your hand would get sore from it?
101090.login: Can you recognize me today, Commander? My sisters don't look like this!
101090.battle: There's only a handful of enemies. Let's beat them with sheer numbers!
101090.feeling2: Whew... I need to take care of my sisters so much that I don't really have time to think about anything else...
101090.mission_complete: I wonder if all my sisters can get an equal share of the rewards...
101090.main: Last time someone tried to impersonate me, one of my little sisters told them to name EVERY Fletcher-class ship. That's when they gave up the act~|When I look at my little sisters, it makes me wonder... Maybe our parents were rabbits?|... Commander? Really... Are you thinking about one of my sisters again?
101090.feeling5: Hm? You want to help me take care of my little sisters? There's a lot of them, and I could use the help, but... Are you really, REALLY sure? In that case... Can I think about it for a bit first...?
101090.upgrade: Now I can take better care of my sisters!
101090.unlock: Hm? You think we've met before? I get it... You know, I have over 100 sisters who look like me! I'll be following your orders from now on, Commander.
101090.feeling4: Out of all of us in the fleet... Who do you personally like the most, Commander? ... Counting me as well?
101090.feeling1: S-sorry, I have to go check up on my little sisters...
101090.propose: A family, huh? ... I already have so many sisters, but you're special to me after all, Commander!
101090.drop_descrip: Fletcher-class destroyer - Fletcher, Hull Number DD-445!
101090.profile: I'm Fletcher, the big sister of all 175 Fletcher-class destroyers! As the main force of the destroyer fleet, I participated in all the important naval battles~
101090.touch2: C-Commander, please stop! What if my sisters see this...
101090.mission: I can go on missions with my sisters again. Give the order whenever you're ready, Commander!
101090.home: I'm back~ Wait, huh? Did another one of my little sisters join the fleet while I was gone?
101090.win_mvp: I've heard that if you collect fifteen stars then one of your wishes will come true~!
101090.expedition: A commission has been completed! Let's see what's next... Wow, there's so many! Almost one for each of my little sisters...
101090.mail: Who has been writing so many letters to you, Commander? I'm a bit curious...
101090.feeling3: Commander, can you help me a little bit? Thank you... You're stronger than me, after all... I'm a little jealous.
101090.lose: *Sob*... You bullies... My sisters will hurt you if they find out about this!

303070.detail: Commander, acquiring intel is the first step to victory.
303070.touch: I'm supervising the destroyers' training right now. Please save it for later if it's not an emergency.
303070.login: Would you like some homemade pancakes, Commander?
303070.battle: Let's see the fruits of my daily training! All guns, open fire!
303070.feeling2: It is not unusual for a weaker force to defeat a stronger one in a naval battle. Victory or defeat is often decided by good judgment and split-second decision making. We must be thorough in our training in order to cultivate these abilities.
303070.headtouch: ... Please do this kind of thing to destroyers, not me...
303070.mission_complete: Don't call it a day after finishing just one mission!
303070.main: If I get another chance... I'd like to pet Hatsukaze's head again.|I've put on weight?! Commander... there are some things that even you shouldn't say.|Bergall?! Phew... you were talking about someone else.
303070.feeling5: Commander, I've finished processing those files. It's the end of the day, so why don't we grab dinner together? ... ... How's it taste?
303070.upgrade: I won't let such a small improvement get to my head.
303070.unlock: I am, {namecode:63}, first ship of the {namecode:63}-class heavy cruisers. Commander, is there anything I can help you with?
303070.feeling4: I saw your light on, so I came to check on you. I had no idea you'd still be awake; even being a workaholic should have its limits! Come on, I'm not leaving until you fall asleep.
303070.propose: Commander, your body is no longer just yours alone. Make sure you take care of yourself properly... for me, okay?
303070.drop_descrip: First ship of the {namecode:63}-class heavy cruisers, {namecode:63}.
303070.skill: Burn this final sight into your memory!
303070.profile: I am {namecode:63}, of the Sakura Empire's {namecode:63}-class heavy cruisers. I participated in both the glorious victory of the Java Sea and the humiliating defeat at Leyte Gulf. Afterwards, I was struck by a torpedo and pursued by submarines. In the end, I could only watch from the South as my nation surrendered. It is hard to say whether that was fortune or misfortune. Anyways, Commander, you can always talk to me if something is on your mind.
303070.mission: Commander, please don't hesitate to ask for help!
303070.home: This method of relaxing is inefficient. Why not try some of my specially-made energy drink?
303070.win_mvp: This victory was made possible by everyone's efforts, not just my own!
303070.expedition: Commission complete! Is everyone putting forward their best effort?
303070.mail: New mail has arrived! Is this the latest training manual?
303070.feeling3: Commander, remember to take breaks as needed. Your efficiency will be worse if you run out of stamina... Lap... pillow? It's fine by me... but will it really help you recover faster?
303070.lose: It's all because I neglected my daily training... Everyone, I'm sorry...

308013.detail: Does this outfit excite you? Hehehe~ You can stare all you want, you know~
308013.touch: I picked up a few massage techniques! Hehehe~ Want me to try them on you, Commander?
308013.login: I'm here to serve you for the whole day! Just tell me if there's anything you want me to do~
308013.main: Here! A glass of hot milk for you! Aren't I super duper great?|Commander, which do you like better, bunnies or cats? Hehehe~|Hmm, there's a lot of girls dressed like bunnies right now... I'll try to be your most favorite one!
308013.unlock: I thought I'd try on this bunny costume! Hehehe, do you like it? If you think it's cute, I wanna hear you say it~
308013.drop_descrip: I thought I'd try on this bunny costume! Hehehe, do you like it? If you think it's cute, I wanna hear you say it~
308013.touch2: It feels a little weird, doing this in a bunny outfit...
308013.home: Well done, Commander~ I've been waiting for you here this whole time! Hehehe~ Aren't I great?

303113.detail: Oh no, the ink... Commander, don't step on the paper!
303113.touch: It would be great if I could really bring "Fortune" to Commander and everyone else with my calligraphy.
303113.login: Commander, welcome back. Pardon me for making a mess; I'll clean it up right away.
303113.main: Qipao? Atago picked it out, saying you like this kind of outfit. How is it? |What? "Fortune" is the only thing that needs to be written? I thought I could write whatever I wanted... |Commander, can I try writing your name next? Hm? No particular reason... I just felt like it.
303113.unlock: Calligraphy is also a form of self-cultivation, so I am instructing the children... Commander, would you also like to join?
303113.drop_descrip: Calligraphy is also a form of self-cultivation, so I am instructing the children... Commander, would you also like to join?
303113.touch2: Commander?! I-I won't be able to write like this...!

303112.detail: I may have lost to Miss Saratoga in sandcastle building, but I shall redeem myself in beach volleyball.
303112.touch: The younger girls are all so energetic... Commander, did you know you can tell their age by when they were launched?
303112.login: Of course I can sympathize with the others. In this kind of heat, it is important to get some rest. However, we mustn’t neglect our training!
303112.main: Miss Saratoga wants to challenge me? Fine. Swimming, volleyball... just name it. I’ll take her on.|Atago, did you bring my sunglasses?|Relax, Commander. I didn’t bring this kendo sword to hit you with. It’s because I heard that someone from the Royal Navy is going to be here. Heh, just kidding. It’s because Atago is scared of ghosts~
303112.unlock: Commander, even I’ll get embarrassed if you keep staring at me like that... Eh? Why did I bring a volleyball? Did you not order me to bring it?
303112.drop_descrip: Commander, even I’ll get embarrassed if you keep staring at me like that... Eh? Why did I bring a volleyball? Did you not order me to bring it?
303112.touch2: Don’t touch me! I’m working on a sand castle... it has to be at least 70% bigger than Sara’s!
303112.home: Good work, Commander. ...What? Miss Saratoga is going to join Team Royal during the beach volleyball tournament? I see... a chance for payback has come!

900004.detail: Before and after the modernization of the data is much worse!
900004.login: Commander, you're back! Me? I'm looking at the clouds.
900004.feeling2: Mmhmm, the weather is nice, it's weather suitable for going out for recon at sea~ Commander you want to come together?
900004.mission_complete: Commander! How could you forget to collect your mission rewards?
900004.main: I'm always like this! I've got to explore before I find a place I like.|Commander, want to watch the clouds with me? I bet we'll see wonderful things!|Don't look at me like that. I've been to plenty of places before!
900004.feeling5: Although I'm happy when praised by other people, now whenever I can assist Commander, I feel even happier, why is that...
900004.upgrade: If you get lost again, you can protect yourself.
900004.unlock: Where is this place... Ah, hello! You're the Commander? I'm Suffolk. I've finally found you!
900004.feeling4: My elder sisters are very strong, I would be happy if only I could assist them~Eh, I'm worked hard? Ehehe, I got praised~
900004.propose: Hng hng, commander finally noticed the shining spot hidden underneath my woozy appearance! From now on I can be as lazy as I want...ehh, I can't?...
900004.profile:
I'm the fifth ship of the Kent-class, Suffolk.
Don't judge me by my looks! I'll be your go to ship whenever a critical moment comes. You know I basically saved the day at the Denmark Strait!
900004.touch2: ...Aah, Commander! Say something if you're here.
900004.mission: The weather sure is nice... Oh? Commander! You've got some new missions.
900004.home: Good work commander, want a cup of tea?
900004.win_mvp: Wow that cloud looks like...ehh, we won?
900004.expedition: This cloud looks like cotton candy...hmm? Ahh, Commander, Commission team is back~
900004.mail: Commander...ehh, what did I want to say...ahh, yes, new mail!
900004.feeling3: Reconnaissance is a very important task! Eh, losing focus? Wh-what are you saying, I'm just ob-observing the weather.
900004.lose: Wuu...if only I paid more attention.

305121.detail: Hey Suruga, let's go somewhere– Come on, don't be all "I like it indoors" and "I'd rather not draw attention," just come out and enjoy the summer with us!
305121.touch: Want to head to that other area? I'll come with you.
305121.login: There you are, at last. Want to get something to eat, if you're hungry? Like dumplings, or a rice ball, or something.
305121.main: Akashi sure got that vending machine and stall set up quick... She's ingenious, but only when there's money to be made...|Why the hesitation? It's just a pool. Nothing wrong with just swimming together with me, is there?|Really looks like Amagi, Akagi, and all the rest are enjoying the summer. All thanks to you, Commander. You should be proud.
305121.unlock: Refreshing drinks, delicious food, warm sunshine... and a pool to beat the heat? Heh, isn't this the essence of summer?
305121.drop_descrip: Refreshing drinks, delicious food, warm sunshine... and a pool to beat the heat? Heh, isn't this the essence of summer?
305121.home: Whoa, this drink is really good. Want a taste, Commander? Hehehe~

404010.detail: Only those who have not been scarred would laugh at someone else's.
404010.login: You're back? Good timing. I'm just about to test my guns.
404010.battle: Let us trample the shattered remnants of our enemies!
404010.hp_warning: I shall fight until the last bullet!
404010.feeling2: If only I didn't need to care about anything other than becoming stronger or defeating more enemies. But, reality isn't so simple...
404010.mission_complete: Rewards? Hah, now that's what I'm looking forward to.
404010.main: Those lightweight aircraft carriers simply can't match our combat abilities!|Do me a favor and remind our friends not to sail directly in front of me... I might not be able to resist firing at them...|"The Ugly Sisters"? Hmph, it's not a bad name... Sounds like a good name for this war, too...
404010.feeling5: I've never retreated - not because I'm fearless, but because I've always had a reason to keep fighting. In the past, it was for the Iron Blood. Now, it's for your sake, Commander... I mean, your fleet's sake!
404010.upgrade: I'm looking forward to the next battle!
404010.unlock: In Scharnhorst's dictionary, the word "retreat" simply doesn't exist! You're the Commander? Let me see what you've got.
404010.feeling4: Hey there, Commander! I just went to train with the other girls. Everyone is full of energy, all thanks to how reliable you are. I'm really taking a liking to this place.
404010.feeling1: Cowards have no right to stand on the battlefield!
404010.propose: Don't worry. For the fleet, and for you, Commander, I'll learn to protect myself and be less reckless than before. But, as always, please continue counting on me for combat!
404010.skill: Anton, Bruno, Caesar... Cannons at the ready!
404010.profile: I’m Scharnhorst. I will stand until the last moment of any battle. This is my determination, as well as my pride. Leave all the fighting to me!
404010.touch2: Stand right there, Commander. If you can take a shot from me, I'll forgive you...
404010.mission: Missions? Let's take care of them in one fell swoop.
404010.home: Not bad at all. Seems like you're getting used to battle.
404010.win_mvp: If there's anything worthy of my trust, it's my cannon!
404010.expedition: A commission has been completed. Seriously, you ought to let me and my little sister handle this stuff.
404010.mail: You've got mail, Commander. You're quite the popular one, aren't you?
404010.feeling3: You've got a pretty nice fleet here. Being here makes me feel like giving it my all.

103138.detail: Oww! Son of a...! Learning how to cook sucks! Can't believe Vincennes told me to do this when all she does is microwave her food... But I'll keep trying! Just for the Commander!
103138.touch: Yeah? What is i– Huh?! S-seriously, I've told you not to randomly go "I love you" around me! I'm so embarrassed I could die!
103138.login: You wanna go on a hunt again, Commander? Or a sortie, that's fine too!
103138.battle: Walk right into my trap, you scrapheaps!
103138.main: You serious?! Now that we're married, we're gonna be cleaning the office together?!|I'll be here the whole day if you need me, Commander!|Anything I could help out with, Commander? Like, c'mon, we're wed and I'm your secretary. Put me to work doing more stuff if you want.
103138.unlock: Commander, why's that Quincy so happy to see me in this outfit? It's hard to move around in, and there's all this stuff flapping around that makes it hard to hunt. What do you think of this outfit?
103138.drop_descrip: Commander, why's that Quincy so happy to see me in this outfit? It's hard to move around in, and there's all this stuff flapping around that makes it hard to hunt. What do you think of this outfit?
103138.touch2: S-s-s-so this kinda thing's fine now, huh?
103138.home: "Welcome home, Honey♪" – Urgh! Stupid Astoria, forcing me to say this cheesy crap... It's not my style, for crying out loud... Huh?! C-Commander?!
103138.lose: Sorry for this, Commander. But I'll get 'em next time!

107032.detail: It's a little bit hard to play pranks on people with an outfit like this, what should I do... Woah! Commander, when'd you get here!
107032.touch: Commander, I hope your attention isn't focused on some place weird?
107032.login: Welcome back, Commander~! The prank this time... is a perfectly ordinary and prank-free greeting~!
107032.main: Sure enough, a black ribbon suits Sister sara the best! |As a special service for the hardworking commander... Sister Sara's smile will wash away your fatigue! How do you feel? Teehee~ |Commander, what are you fantasizing about right now? C'mon, you can tell me!
107032.unlock: Hey everyone~! This time, Sister Sara has brought you fashion from a faraway land! Commander, what do you think of it?
107032.drop_descrip: Hey everyone~! This time, Sister Sara has brought you fashion from a faraway land! Commander, what do you think of it?
107032.touch2: Woah! Commander, what are you trying to do to your cute little Sara?

101312.detail: Huh? I don't get the day off on Christmas? ... Fine, give me five more minutes... Just five more minutes... Zzzzz...
101312.mission_complete: Commander, come check which one of these boxes contains the mission rewards... I forgot which it was...
101312.main: What I want for Christmas...? Don't really care, as long as I can get enough sleep...|Going out on an errand? Have fun... You want me to come with you? I don't wanna...|Helena, wanna take a nap together? It's really snug inside this box...
101312.feeling5: I didn't intend to doze off in here, but seeing your face first thing in the morning is pretty nice... Merry Christmas, Commander...
101312.unlock: Merry Christmas, Commander... I'm your present, probably... Would you mind closing the lid for me so I can sleep a bit more... Zzz...
101312.drop_descrip: Merry Christmas, Commander... I'm your present, probably... Would you mind closing the lid for me so I can sleep a bit more... Zzz...
101312.home: You tired, Commander? Here, borrow half my pillow...

301351.detail: Commander, I had a dream. Everyone was playing together hand-in-hand, and nobody was fighting! It was really fun!
301351.touch: Ehehe~ Commander, your hand is so warm! Commander, sing me a lullaby~
301351.main: It's no good that Commander does all the work while I sleep... I'll also help... Zzzzzz...|Commander, want to play house? Yes, these are plushies of Mutsuki and Kisaragi! |Commander, come here if you're tired! You can have half the pillow!
301351.unlock: *yawn* ... Kisaragi, Mutsuki, let's take a nap together... Commander? Do you want to join too?
301351.drop_descrip: *yawn* ... Kisaragi, Mutsuki, let's take a nap together... Commander? Do you want to join too?
301351.mission: Commander, I'm coming with you on your mission! Don't leave me behind...!
301351.expedition: Urgh... the alarm clock... is freakin' annoying... Ah, wait! It's the commission timer! Commander!
301351.mail: Mail? Oh, I stuffed it under the pillow and forgot about it...!

301721.detail: Commander, come ski with me... Yeah, bring the Manjuus too...!
301721.touch: Eep?! Commander, your hands are cold...
301721.login: The best thing about winter... is skiing in the snow!
301721.main: Today, I will transform into a snow bunny! |The snow is so sparkly and soft... it's very fun. |You shouldn't underestimate me~ I've been practicing this whole time.
301721.unlock: It's snowing...! I've finished rallying the forces... so let us advance!
301721.drop_descrip: It's snowing...! I've finished rallying the forces... so let us advance!
301721.touch2: My outfit is thick, therefore wholesome...

902010.detail: You lookin' to have some fun? You mean with me, or my weapon?
902010.touch: Touch me all you want! As long as you don't mind getting hurt.
902010.login: Finally! You're back! I thought I was gonna rust up from boredom while you were gone. Gimme a task, any task, and I'll do it.
902010.battle: I'm lookin' for a fun time... Gimme one!
902010.hp_warning: Hell yeah! More of that! This is getting fun!
902010.feeling2: Lookin' to be a boring day like any other...
902010.mission_complete: You finished a mission? Cool, that's quicker than I expected. Maybe I underestimated you, Commander.
902010.main: Just sitting in the office, boooored out of my mind while the Commander goes ham on a ton of paperwork. *siiigh*...|If the goal's to beat the enemy, then what's wrong with me bashing them with my rigging? I swear, you fuss over the strangest stuff, Commander.|Can't say I'm keen on planning stuff... It's like, you make a plan, but it always changes, y'know?
902010.feeling5: My opinion on you? Hmm, to tell you the truth, I kinda like you. You wanna hang out and do something fun sometime? I mean, we already have fun every day, but still!
902010.upgrade: Makes me look back on my days in Brest...
902010.unlock: Vichya, Sardegna, Iron Blood... and now this place? Ah well, doesn't matter to me 'long as I get to have a good time. Anyway, I'm La Galissonnière from the Vichya Dominion. Nice meetin' you!
902010.feeling4: Sure, we ships fire our guns and torpedoes all day, but it's fun to just have a chat about weapons now and then. Hit me up for that sometime, Commander! You seem like a cool person!
902010.feeling1: If you wanna quit being a commander, I could refer you to a decent new job.
902010.propose: You're just the kind of person I love, Commander! Hahahah! From now on, if anyone tries to mess with you, I'm gonna deal with 'em!
902010.drop_descrip: La Galissonnière-class light cruiser – La Galissonnière.
902010.profile: I was assigned to Vichya's "High Seas Force" back during the war, I think? Don't think I ever set sail though, due to fuel shortages... Y'know what? You're probably gonna get a quicker rundown if you just ask Dunkerque.
902010.touch2: Listen, unlike a certain someone from the Templar Knights, "dirty work" is my specialty... Wanna know more?
902010.mission: These missions are a pain? Well, sorry to hear that? I can't exactly do 'em for you, y'know.
902010.home: Sorry, nobody's permitted to enter the office while the Commander is out... Oh, hey, Commander! Obviously you can come on in!
902010.win_mvp: Ahaha! Now that was a lot of fun!
902010.expedition: Commission team's back, eh? Cool, then I'll go say hi since I've got nothing better to do.
couple_encourage: Could you make me another mousse cake when we get back?
Cardinal, I march into battle beneath your banner.
902010.mail: Here, letter for you. Better read it now, 'cause it's not my problem if you lose it.
902010.feeling3: I've got some of Dunkerque's handmade mousse cake! Here, have a slice. Nah, nah, don't thank me, thank the girl who made it!
902010.lose: Oops, I've been beaten... Just let me fight another time!

305052.detail: Th-there's no need to be in a hurry to go outside, right...? It's spacious, quiet, and warm here... and you are authorized to pat my fluffy friend.
305052.touch: Do you wish to comment upon my attire? Hehe, don't underestimate the skill of the Sakura Empire's craftspeople!
305052.login: What do you plan to do today? Do call upon me if you need my help.
305052.main: The moon can be freely enjoyed throughout the year, but there are few opportunities for the two of us to gaze at the moon together... |Mutsu? Let her go out and play. Unlike Kawakaze, she has no awareness of her surroundings... Ah, b-but don't let her hear I said that!|Moon-viewing sake? This has indeed been quite popular, but I... Ah, f-forget it! If you want to drink, then treat yourself! ...after all, I'm not allowed to...
305052.feeling5: C-Commander, I, um... "th-the moon is beautiful tonight...!" Gyaaah...! It's way too embarrassing... there's no way I could say that...
305052.unlock: Perfect, you have arrived. As long as you are here, the usual moon-watching will prove to be much more enjoyable... Why don't you stay here today and rest for a while?
305052.drop_descrip: Perfect, you have arrived. As long as you are here, the usual moon-watching will prove to be much more enjoyable... Why don't you stay here today and rest for a while?
305052.home: Kawakaze, prepare a cushion for the Commander. It would be inappropriate for only me to be comfortable.
305052.win_mvp: Prostrate yourself before the might of the Sakura Empire!

807011.detail: Everyone seems to be enjoying themselves at the beach. What do you say about playing beach volleyball, or building a sandcastle, Commander? Me, I would rather remain here and observe.
807011.touch: Your praise honors me, but I can easily imagine that you praise everyone here for their swimsuits.
807011.login: Would you like a swim ring, Commander? It could be useful if you plan on playing with the girls by the beach.
807011.main: One can seek cover from the sun, but cannot escape the heat. As I'm on lifeguard duty, perhaps I should've brought an electric fan with me.|This ice cream is going to melt if nobody eats it. Say, Commander, would you like a taste?|Both Vichya and Iris girls enjoying the summer on the same beach... A lovely sight, in my opinion.
807011.unlock: Are you perhaps feeling unwell, Commander? Oh, I see, you're just looking for a shaded place to rest? Acknowledged. In that case, you may sit here if you'd like.
807011.drop_descrip: Are you perhaps feeling unwell, Commander? Oh, I see, you're just looking for a shaded place to rest? Acknowledged. In that case, you may sit here if you'd like.
807011.touch2: I suspected you would engage in obscene behavior as soon as you distanced yourself from onlookers, Commander...
807011.home: You were out at sea? Here, have a towel.

305081.detail: You should avoid swimming too much as you're so sickly, Amagi. How tragic it is, a ship such as you being so frail...
305081.login: Whew... It's nice to get to play freely, but I must take heed of all the extra attention this swimsuit draws to me...
305081.main: The shrine maiden and her sister, frolicking in the water... A rare sight to be had.|We could play a round of go if you are bored. I want a new opponent after playing against only my sister for so long.|You're in need of a snack? Sorry, I only just got these from my sister. That said... we could exchange side dishes, I suppose...
305081.unlock: An inspection? ...You're awfully gung-ho about your work considering how hot it is outside... Surely you wouldn't have some sort of ulterior motive?
305081.drop_descrip: An inspection? ...You're awfully gung-ho about your work considering how hot it is outside... Surely you wouldn't have some sort of ulterior motive?
305081.touch2: Try this with my sister instead. Actually, don't; it would likely backfire on you...
305081.home: My sister is still on the way here? Hmph, then I will prepare you some food.

301210.detail: C-Commander, um... I-I'm glad you're c-checking in on me, but...
301210.touch: I need to talk with you more oft... Eek?!
301210.login: *Cries*... I can't possibly be a secretary...
301210.battle: I-I'll give it all I've got!
301210.feeling2: C-Commander, do you think it's possible for me to get over my fear of s-strangers...?
301210.mission_complete: C-Commander, our rewards ha... Huh?! N-no, I don't need any!
301210.main: I miss my sisters so much...|C-Commander... p-please don't stare at me so much...|I-I'm quite timid, b-but I'll work really hard! ... I hope...
301210.feeling5: C-Commander! I-I just managed to have a normal conversation with someone else! I'm so relieved... I-it's all thanks to you, Commander...
301210.upgrade: I hope I can be of service to everyone...
301210.unlock: I-i-it's nice to meet you, I-I'm Hatsuha... U-um... P-please don't stare at me so much...!
301210.feeling4: *Sob*... I can't, I-I can't do it! ... B-but maybe I can hold a conversation with you, Commander...
301210.feeling1: C-Commander, i-if you get any closer then I'll s-shoot you!
301210.propose: O-overcoming my timid nature is going to take a lot of time, but I'm not anxious anymore... Because I know you'll always be with me, Commander...
301210.skill: P-please get out of the way, everyone...!
301210.profile: I-I'm {namecode:30}, first ship of t-the {namecode:30}-class... I-I served in the north, together with my s-sisters from Destroyer Division 21... I didn't achieve much, b-b-but I tried my best...
301210.mission: C-Commander! Um, well... you shouldn't ignore your m-missions!
301210.home: C-C-Commander, g-g-great work...! I-I finally managed to say it!
301210.expedition: Commander, um, the commission team is back... I-I should go greet them? N-n-n-no, there's no way!
couple_encourage: F-follow me!
301210.feeling3: Umm, C-Commander... C-can I ask you to be my... conversation practice partner...? I-I... want to make friends with everyone in the fleet...
301210.lose: *Cries*... I really am not suited for combat...

307050.detail: The melody of my flute is a requiem for the dead. Shall I play it for you?
307050.touch: Commander, would you like to hear me play my flute?
307050.login: Intelligence is said to be a woman’s virtue, but that often puts me at odds with those senpai of mine. How troublesome~
307050.battle: The perfected aircraft carrier, {namecode:95}, setting sail!
307050.hp_warning: Pump water to the other side! Hurry!
307050.feeling2: My sister {namecode:96} and I held on for two years during the darkest of times. If only our senpai could have worked a little bit harder.
307050.mission_complete: We’re not going to carry out our plans of attrition warfare? Tch~
307050.main: To always be dealing with those senpai from the First Carrier Division... Commander, you must have a really strong liver.|Though our relationship was once one of victim and perpetrator, I look forward to working with you, Lexington.|{namecode:96}, if you keep causing trouble for our Eagle Union colleagues, you’ll only get tempura for dinner tonight~
307050.feeling5: Commander, could you lend me your shoulder? Sometimes, even I want to simply clear my mind and rest. When I get like that, can I depend on you to be by my side?
307050.unlock: As the flagship of the Fifth Carrier Division, I, Shoukaku, shall do my best to become as good as those esteemed senpai in the First Carrier Division, or something... *giggles* That was on purpose~
307050.feeling4: Those senpai are so sly! Just when I was about to overtake them, they went somewhere I could never reach! How unfair!
307050.feeling1: I think I just saw a future in which you were cut down by {namecode:91}, Commander.
307050.propose: The melody of my flute is like a flowing river, requiring an inspiration that usually can only be found atop a mountain. Just being by your side, however, inspires me even more.
307050.drop_descrip: First ship of the {namecode:95}-class aircraft carriers, {namecode:95}.
307050.skill: This is the privilege of being the elder sister!
307050.profile: I am {namecode:95}, the flagship of the Fifth Carrier Division. Because my super smart senpai went and got themselves all killed, I had to carry the flag of the Sakura Empire’s carrier divisions. Though I was more accomplished than them, for whatever reason, I was always considered weaker. Maybe it was due to my "lack of grace and speed" during my final moments... With that said, allow me to reintroduce myself. I am Shoukaku, the punching bag of the Sakura Empire. Please take care of me from now on~
307050.touch2: Commander, come and indulge yourself in {namecode:95}'s tenderness.
307050.mission: Let me take a look the mission... It’s not the Coral Sea? That’s too bad~
307050.home: The girls have returned safely to port, just like the Fifth Carrier Division always does.
307050.win_mvp: The Glory of the 5th Carrier Divison is here! *giggles*
307050.expedition: This is all required to carry out the Circle Five Plan.
couple_encourage: {namecode:96}, give it your all! I'll cover you!
Do you see my true power, {namecode:91}?
This time... I'll prove to you how powerful I really am!
I won't be able to protect you if you stray too far!
Where is the Queen of the Docks heading to?
307050.mail: We’ve got mail from HQ, they told us to carry out the Decisive Battle Doctrine. Heh, just kidding~!
307050.feeling3: Do I hold a grudge against the First and Second Carrier Divisions? Of course~ For them to leave us behind like that, wouldn’t anyone complain in that situation?
307050.lose: Hiryuu-senpai may be willing to fight until the bitter end, but... that’s not my style. What a shame~

301211.detail: This is... a rabbit made of snow... I-It's still not done! ... But... making various things out of snow... i-is fun...
301211.touch: If it's with the Commander, this time... this time for sure... with everyone...!
301211.login: U-Um! ... I-I've already gotten u-used to Commander's gaze, so I'm okay! But... b-being stared at... I-I really can't...
301211.main: Eyes, eyebrows, and a nose... Just a little bit more... | W-Wakaba? T-The snow at home port isn't c-covered in pine nuts... | S-Snowball fight?! It's im-impossible for me! ...Hau...
301211.feeling5: B-Being with the Commander, is so warm... it seems that it makes even the cold of the snow f-fine... I-I feel like I'll also be able to talk properly with everyone else...
301211.unlock: Everyone's playing together...? I-I think I'll pass... Y-you want me to join them? Ugh, well, if you say so, then I-I-I'll try to socialize with them...!
301211.drop_descrip: Everyone's playing together...? I-I think I'll pass... Y-you want me to join them? Ugh, well, if you say so, then I-I-I'll try to socialize with them...!
301211.touch2: Wah?! Th-This is... unhh... (It looks like Hatsuharu fainted again)
301211.home: A snowman... Somehow, I was able to finish it...

207011.detail: I've come well prepared in hopes of learning the ropes of our infirmary.
207011.touch: Let's take your temperature, just to be sure. Mind if I assist with that?
207011.login: Debrief me on your symptoms. Oh, that doesn't sound like what a doctor would say? Then how about... Do you feel ill?
207011.main: I've come up with a new, healthy diet that improves your physical stamina. Care to give it a try?|Treating wounds and saving lives – being a doctor comes with great responsibility, but also great pride.|Are you scared of needles, Commander? I understand. Then as part of this training, we should give you a shot, just so– Oh, okay, maybe we shouldn't.
207011.unlock: This may be an exercise, but even so I will give it my all. Right now, I am not just a Royal Navy warrior, but a medical resident as well. If you ever feel ill, come see me, Commander.
207011.drop_descrip: This may be an exercise, but even so I will give it my all. Right now, I am not just a Royal Navy warrior, but a medical resident as well. If you ever feel ill, come see me, Commander.
207011.touch2: Umm... Are you feeling lightheaded, Commander? Do you need a thorough examination?
207011.home: "Weight Loss and Health Care Metholody," eh... Oh, ahem! Good to see you again, Commander. I-I was just reading medical literature, that's all!

801041.detail: It is undignified to stare so much at a maiden's swimsuit. B-besides, it's really embarrassing...
801041.touch: Commander... you didn't get heatstroke, did you?
801041.login: Jeez, how'd my glasses end up in the sand... Um, where's my handkerchief... ah, there it is! Oh, Commander, when did you get here?
801041.main: If only there was a spell to make it cool down... maybe something to blot out the sun? Hehe, just kidding. A cold drink will suffice. Commander, what would you like? |The sheer number of people gathered here... is this the mystical allure of the summertime beach? |Commander, have you seen Temeraire? ...She's playing beach volleyball with the others? Hehe, I see she's as full of energy as ever.
801041.unlock: It is said that the summertime sea holds an extraordinary enchantment over people... but the only supernatural thing I'm feeling is this accursed heat... Am I missing something?
801041.drop_descrip: It is said that the summertime sea holds an extraordinary enchantment over people... but the only supernatural thing I'm feeling is this accursed heat... Am I missing something?
801041.touch2: Do you want to be turned into a starfish?
801041.home: Everyone was saying how they wanted to head to the beach because of how hot it is, but it doesn't seem any cooler out here... Ugh...

301331.touch: Commander... let's have some snacks together?
301331.main: I also... want to play with everyone else... |It's a new year... I've gotta try hard to make... um, make ten new friends! |Y-Yuudachi, can I also... join the snow fight?
301331.unlock: Uh... umm... Commander, is Kisaragi's new outfit... p-pretty? This year, um... Kisaragi wants to work real hard too!
301331.drop_descrip: Uh... umm... Commander, is Kisaragi's new outfit... p-pretty? This year, um... Kisaragi wants to work real hard too!

901019.detail: Commander, are you that desperate to see my gallant form as I unload all my cannons and torpedo tubes? Ehehe, what am I going to do with you~
901019.touch: Hehe, how about I be the one to give you a shoulder massage this time?
901019.login: My torpedoes and cannons are locked and loaded! Commander, I'm ready to sortie at any time!
901019.main: Hehe! Commander, is this victory pose cool? I saw it in an anime! |Commission or sortie, I'm ready to do anything! With how strong I am now, I won't let you down, Commander! |Is there something that needs doing? I'll be happy to shoulder even a little bit of your burdens.
901019.unlock: Retro~ fit~ com~ plete! The new and improved Le Mars is at your service~!
901019.drop_descrip: Retro~ fit~ com~ plete! The new and improved Le Mars is at your service~!
901019.home: Welcome back, Commander! Shall we plan our next sortie?
901019.win_mvp: Now, for a victory pose! ...Hey! Wait for meeee!

206060.detail: The big mirror in my room? What about it? If I told you, "I just like mirrors," would that satisfy your curiosity?
206060.touch: Maybe try finishing your work before you "chat me up" or "interview me" or however you wanna sugarcoat it?
206060.login: There's some saying that goes, "the early bird catches the worm." ...If that's true, I guess you'd starve, Commander.
206060.battle: Careful, now. The battlefield is no place to worry about fuel economy.
206060.hp_warning: ...I can't afford to mess around, huh.
206060.feeling2: I can hear just fine, Commander, so don't go yelling in my ear, thanks...
206060.mission_complete: Those mission rewards will expire if you don't claim them. Maybe.
206060.main: If you need my help with something, just say it. You do need to try and accomplish it on your own first, though.|Work is like food, in a way; leave it sitting for too long and it goes bad. Just so you know.|I heard Yuubari and Akashi get up to fun experiments in the lab. I kind of wanna see one. Kind of.
206060.feeling5: How would I describe you? I dunno, I guess like a storm in the middle of a peaceful voyage... No, no, I didn't mean it like that... Sorry, what I meant to say is, um...
206060.upgrade: Thanks a bunch... Well, yeah, didn't you want a thank-you?
206060.unlock: I'm Perseus, from the Royal Navy. You can pronounce it "Per-see-us" if you want though... Well, whatever. Are we done here? Great. Nice meeting you.
206060.feeling4: I'm a total moron... Why am I so rude to the Commander when I just want to be friends... I'm so, so stupid...
206060.feeling1: You really are like a can of rancid surströmming.
206060.propose: Obviously I don't hate you, Commander. How could I, when I adore talking to you and being patted on the head? L-look, I'm trying to say... I love you. I mean it...
206060.drop_descrip: Colossus-class light aircraft carrier – Perseus (HMS Perseus.)
206060.profile: I'm Perseus, the Colossus-class light aircraft carrier. Sadly, I didn't enter service until the war had ended. Don't have much in the way of a reputation or experience as a result. Still, I'll try to do a good job. All right, is that good enough? *sigh*...
206060.touch2: You must really want a seat at the naval jailhouse dinner table, huh?
206060.mission: What kind of lazy cat are you, just lounging around all day instead of doing missions?
206060.home: One quick battle, and you're knackered already, Commander? You have the stamina of a beached whale.
206060.win_mvp: Looks like the enemy will have to, uh, try harder next time.
206060.expedition: Look, Commander... No, I'm not angry, I was just going to tell you a commission is done.
couple_encourage: Time for a new experiment?
206060.mail: You've got mail. Nope, didn't bring it with me. Next time, ask, and I'll consider it.
206060.feeling3: If you ask me, people should be able to say whatever they want... Oh, hello there, Commander. Just talking to myself.

899012.detail: Let us also give our utmost this coming year, as to not squander the preparations everyone has painstakingly made.
899012.login: Bonjour, Commander. Please determine the duty you would like to fulfill first today.
899012.battle: Be cleansed in the Iris's light!
899012.main: The Dragon Empery's Spring Festival... the celebration of a new year seems quintessential to all. Please rest well after completing your work.|La Galissonnière... seems to be thoroughly enjoying this holiday. Rather, that girl seems to be able to find enjoyment in just about anything. Quite broad-minded of her.|The greatest joy is to be able to have a life of peace. If everyone can act in accordance with God's will, then there would be no need for justicars.
899012.unlock: Commander, regarding your next appointment... Ah, hard work is one of the highest virtues of the Iris's holy knights. On weekdays or vacations, in knights' armor or the Dragon Empery's attire, there can be no pause to my prayer, my training, or my duties as the administrator of your will.
899012.drop_descrip: Commander, regarding your next appointment... Ah, hard work is one of the highest virtues of the Iris's holy knights. On weekdays or vacations, in knights' armor or the Dragon Empery's attire, there can be no pause to my prayer, my training, or my duties as the administrator of your will.
899012.mission: Here are today's assignments. Let's work together to finish them quickly.
899012.home: God witnesses all your deeds. The trials you endure today will surely bear fruit in the future.
899012.expedition: Commander, our comrades-in-arms have returned from their commission. Let us take over their responsibilities so that they may enjoy the Spring Festival.

201330.detail: A change of clothes for the commander, the menus for tomorrow's meals... Oh, Commander. When did you get here? ...Don't mind me, I'm just doing some daily preparations~♪
201330.touch: Was there something you wanted me to do?
201330.login: Commander, did you just arrive? Hehe. There are documents on your desk. I'll have your tea ready in just a moment, so please get started on your work.
201330.hp_warning: My torpedoes still aren't ready... I can hold out for a bit longer...!
201330.feeling2: Commander, I've sworn to protect you and everyone else at the port. I'll use all my might to destroy anything that dares to hurt you!
201330.headtouch: Hehehe. You know, this feels kind of nice.
201330.mission_complete: The mission's been completed! How wonderful!
201330.main: Commander, please let me know when you head out! Whether it's an umbrella or a coat, I'll be sure to have it ready for you.|Eskimo looks like she wants some attention... Commander, I'll do something about her, so please focus on your work. ...That's right, I can call Abercrombie over!|I guess destroyers really have their limits... If only I had bigger guns or torpedoes... Oh, I was just talking to myself. Please don't mind me!
201330.feeling5: "You, who are like the sun, make me feel your warmth just by being there. You, who are like the sun, make me afraid of being swallowed by your warmth." Commander, can I come... a bit closer to you?
201330.upgrade: Mmh~ One step closer to achieving overwhelming firepower... Err, I mean, I'll be more useful to the commander!
201330.unlock: Well met, Commander. I am Icarus, I-class destroyer from the Royal Navy. I specialize in escort and anti-submarine operations. I look forward to working with you.
201330.feeling4: Mm... The more I stay by your side, the more I want to do your work in your stead... Do you think I'm getting a bit too attached to you...?
201330.feeling1: ...If you keep this up, I'll be the only one left who's willing to keep looking after you, Commander...
201330.propose: Just as I've become unable to part with you, have you come to feel the same way about me? I'm so happy! From now on, I'll be sure... to ask you for lots of things♪
201330.profile: My history as a ship...? I escorted Hood and Warspite, and also participated in anti-submarine missions... Basically, I've been here and there and done this and that. I guess you could say I have quite a bit of experience? That being the case, feel free to call upon me, whether in battle or otherwise!
201330.touch2: I-I'm not sure if we should be doing this...
201330.mission: There's a new mission. Let's do our best!
201330.home: Welcome back, Commander. I cleaned up the room while you were away. ...N-no, there's no need to praise me. It really wasn't a big deal!
201330.win_mvp: We won! It's all thanks to you, Commander!
201330.expedition: Commander, would you like me to go greet the commissions team in your stead?
couple_encourage: Miss Hood, this time, I'll defend you properly!
It seems we're heading out together again!
201330.mail: I've finished sorting out the new mail! Should I bring it over?
201330.feeling3: Commander, haven't you been working a bit too hard recently? You need to make sure to get some rest when you can... If you fly too close to the sun, your wings will melt, and you'll fall down, you know? ...Huh? What am I saying...?
201330.lose: If only I could have shot another volley of torpedoes...

101021.detail: What's in this notebook? Well, um... It's a story about a girl chasing after the person she longs for the most in her dream... Y-you want to read it? Fine... Ah, um! Please promise to keep it a secret from Miss Lexington!
101021.touch: C-Commander, please don't play with my floaty ring. You're going to get my notebook wet...
101021.login: According to the weather forecast, it's gonna be real sunny today.
101021.main: If you want to know where Saratoga is, I think I saw her playing beach volleyball with the others?|I seem to be a bit too tired to swim... so I'll just enjoy the feeling of rocking around in this floaty ring...|Does anyone need any help? ...Thank goodness, looks like everyone is doing well...
101021.unlock: Saratoga went over there, and Lexington is... Oh, Commander, good morning! Are you here to play with us, or were you just out for some fresh air...?
101021.drop_descrip: Saratoga went over there, and Lexington is... Oh, Commander, good morning! Are you here to play with us, or were you just out for some fresh air...?
101021.home: Commander, if you're tired, let me give you a massage.
101021.mail: There's a new announcement. Hopefully it's not a storm warning...!

207023.detail: I can use this gun for ceremonial salutes, as well. I'll put her to good use at the banquet!
207023.touch: Commander, would you like to personally carry out the gun salute? Mind the recoil.
207023.login: The more peaceful and inviting the atmosphere, the more one wants to protect it. What do you think, Commander?
207023.main: Oh those destroyers in their Eastern dresses... Ah, I was just thinking how captivating it all is. These New Year's celebrations really are splendid!|I have already committed everything important about the New Year's programming to memory. If you need anything, Commander, do let me know.|Wherever there is trouble, I shall be there! Such is my solemn oath as guardian of the new year!
207023.unlock: Commander, Happy New Year. Oh no, I'm not going hunting. I'm patrolling the port during the New Year's celebrations. Naturally, I volunteered for the job.
207023.drop_descrip: Commander, Happy New Year. Oh no, I'm not going hunting. I'm patrolling the port during the New Year's celebrations. Naturally, I volunteered for the job.
207023.touch2: My neckline is off? Oh, thank you... Oh my, no, it doesn't go like this, does it?!
207023.home: To be able to watch over the destro– The fleet here, that's the best new year's gift anyone could give me.

213010.detail: I am not the harbinger of death... I am just..... guiding them after their times are up
213010.touch: Allow me to channel forth the whispers of the dead...
213010.login: Commander, I'm always here, awaiting for your summons...
213010.battle: Please remain calm. The darkness will only make the stars shine brighter.
213010.feeling2: It was hard to take care of my sister at the beginning, but I got used to it... used to being alone? I'm just used to the fear of it.
213010.mission_complete: Rewards are but worldly possessions. It makes no difference to me whether you collect them or not.
213010.main: Did you just have an out-of-body experience?|I'll always protect my little sisters.|I have to say, this warmth, I don't dislike it.
213010.feeling5: Where there's light, there's darkness. Wherever you are, I'll be near. This isn't fate but the law of this world... It's nothing, it's just something that I've wanted to say for a long time, if I ever found someone who I truly liked.
213010.upgrade: The purer the darkness, the calmer my mind.
213010.unlock: Commander, is that you? I'm Erebus. I followed your voice and have come from afar.
213010.feeling4: I'm afraid no longer. Being next to you, I'm willing to become the darkness to your light; And if that light were to swallow me... No, even if I was to be devoured, that would be fine too.
213010.feeling1: Commander, if you fall into darkness, know that it will be me hunting your soul...
213010.propose: Shadows chase after light, and light embraces the shadows. I've heard of foolish lovers who erase each other, but who can judge another's love? Isn't that right, Commander?
213010.drop_descrip: Erebus-class monitor – Erebus, Hull Number I02!
213010.profile:
Erebus, my name, sounds surreal?
My predecessor was a ship which carried explorers to the North Pole and never returned... like a journey into the abyss.
Please pay more attention to my sisters!
213010.touch2: ... ... uh... ... I'm sorry, it seems like I was having an out-of-body experience.
213010.mission: You'll experience an eternity of restlessness if you die with incomplete missions.
213010.home: The silence after a battle is divine. Take your time and rest.
213010.win_mvp: Allow me to harvest the souls of our enemies.
213010.expedition: I'm not particularly interested in embarking on commissions... The other girls always say I see weird stuff. I suppose it can't be helped... Anyway, your girls are back!
couple_encourage: Terror, stay close to me.
Vampire, please imbibe wine - I mean, blood - with moderation...
Lady Warspite, I shall support you.
Saru Legion? What a fun name!
213010.mail: Letters are what connect humans. Hold them dear.
213010.feeling3: Whenever I'm afraid, all I have to do is think of my little sister. It gives me the strength to push on. Even though my sister can't be without me, I can't be without her either.
213010.lose: Even if you manage to defeat me, you'll never escape the infinite darkness.

305050.detail: Everyone's faces are full of laughter here... I think I am rather fond of this place!
305050.touch: ...! N-No one has ever dared to lay hands on me in such a manner...
305050.login: Welcome ba... oww, I bit my tongue...
305050.hp_warning: The decisive battle is upon us!
305050.feeling2: What do you require of me? Hmm? I am not doing anything in particular. After I handed the work to Yamato, there is little to do except fight.
305050.mission_complete: The mission rewards... Ngh...! Phew... is it acceptable to leave them here?
305050.main: I despise wars, but... at that time, the choice was not mine to make... |Those who speak lightly of war... do you think they are prepared to face the consequences of their actions? |I shall never forget the smiles on the faces of those people who were saved from calamity. That is the reason why I fight.
305050.feeling5: It is enough to be treasured by one person? Since you were the one who brought me out... I shall have you take responsibility... that is, umm, in other words, I command you to... treasure me... if that is acceptable?
305050.upgrade: I hope... to be able to welcome the day when we can all beat our swords into plowshares...
305050.unlock: I am called Nagato, flagship of the Sakura Empire's Combined Fleet. Are you the one known as the Commander? I shall bear witness to whether or not you have the ability to unite this world.
305050.feeling4: I see! I am less intimidating with my riggings taken off. I certainly do feel lighter... but why does it feel like I've lost something... like when I appointed Yamato to take over as flagship?
305050.feeling1: Your wish... is to repeat the errors of the past once more? Very well... I see...
305050.propose: When I cross the river after the war ends, what awaits me is not a searing white light that engulfs everything, but rather, your warm embrace... There is nothing more that I could ask for...
305050.skill: I am called Nagato... Nagato of the Sakura Empire!
305050.profile: I am the manifestation of the soul of the Sakura Empire, the pride and glory of her warrior spirit. As a Big Seven, I am also the symbol of an era. Open your eyes and bask in my radiance... You may stop basking now, I'm getting a bit sleepy...
305050.mission: Is it acceptable to arrange the itinerary in this manner? I do not quite understand how to do it yet...
305050.home: I have never had to welcome anyone before. Perhaps I shall do so by firing my cannons?
305050.win_mvp: Impudent fools... why did they have to provoke me?
305050.expedition: The commission fleet has returned... H-Hey, I managed to remember the time. Have you no words of praise for me?
couple_encourage: Combined Fleet, crush our enemies!
1st Battleship Division, open fire!
Mutsu, leave your questions for after the battle!
Observe closely this battle of mine, Mikasa!
Akagi, I need your strength as my own!
Hmph...! I have no reason to envy you for those... things!
Amagi, you've inconvenienced the Commander...
Kawakaze, I trust you to lead the way!
305050.mail: What is this piece of paper? "Mail?" I see, it's mail. Shall I read it?
305050.feeling3: I should spend more time with the others? Even if I tried to do that, I would not know how to behave, and they would be afraid of me all the same... Hey, what are you doing... why are you taking off my riggings?!
305050.lose: Ugh... I have failed once again...

901021.detail: The book I last read took place on the beach, if I remember properly... It was a murder mystery on the beach, right?
901021.login: Oh, Commander, good day. Would you like some ice cream?
901021.main: McCall from the Eagle Union and Suffolk from the Royal Navy seem to get along really well. The two of them are pretty funny, hehe. |Vauquelin, I'm not going into the water. I'll just spend a nice, peaceful day on the beach like this. |Commander, aren't you going to change into a swimsuit? ...Um, I'm slightly curious, just a little...
901021.unlock: Commander, you're not going to get into the water? ...Ah, I'm fine right here. To tell you the truth, I once got washed away by the waves, and then got laughed at by Vauquelin... so I'm perfectly fine right here.
901021.touch2: Commander, what's wrong? The ice cream? ...Hyaa?!
901021.win_mvp: I could really go for one of Dunkerque's donuts right about now...
901021.mail: Oh, speaking of letters... I'm so sorry, Commander, I got engrossed in our conversation and totally forgot...

301720.detail: Whenever I ask Kinu if I can borrow her cute mask... she just tells me no way in heck...
301720.login: Could you give me the go-ahead to play now?
301720.feeling2: I keep a collection of cute pets. Stop by again and I'll show you my axofrostl and swolejuu.
301720.mission_complete: Nice work on that serving of missions, Commander. You want more, help yourself.
301720.main: Uranami rhymes with rural mommy. Doodle-loo, nothing better to dooo.|Help friends in need, defeat enemies with speed. That's my little motto.|When I tell folks about the things I like, they all look super weirded out, then they strangerzone me. But oh well.
301720.feeling5: Commander, when I'm with you it feels like I'm a fish in water, a bee that found honey, a ticking time bomb of joy that goes BOOOOM! ...Something in that ballpark, basically.
301720.upgrade: Done enhancy-pantsing yet? C'mawn, I wanna play.
301720.unlock: What am I doing here? ...Hmmm? You're adopting me? Aaaaall righty. You lead-a-dee, I'll follow-a-loo.
301720.feeling4: I'd love to hear some of Prof Commander's interesting little trivia. Tell me something about ghosts.
301720.propose: Promise ring. So glitteryyyy. Can I just keep it on forever? Hehehe... I super love you, Commander.
301720.drop_descrip: Special Type I-class destroyer number 10 – Uranami.
301720.profile: I'm the Type I... No wait, Type II... Last try: middle-of-the-pack destroyer, Uranami. My friends and I in Destroyer Division 19 worked really hard. Okay, serious question: what Type am I, exactly?
301720.mission: One super serving of missions with a diet soda, coming right up.
301720.home: Welcome back, tweety-doo. That's what a Manjuu would say. Yup-yup...
301720.win_mvp: I'm awesome... Or so they say. But why?
301720.expedition: The commission team's back. Oooh, riiight, you already knew that.
couple_encourage: Ayanami, do the demon thingy
Woweee! Super cool!
Aoba, what're you scooping for?
301720.mail: Whoosh, here comes a letter. Aaaand there it is.
301720.feeling3: The massive Meowfficer's super fluffy... I mean, ripped. Built like a fridge!
301720.lose: Time to scamper. Don't wanna be left behind.

303090.detail: No matter how much you stare at me, I won't get any stronger... Commander, wouldn't it be better for me to sortie?
303090.touch: I got this from Myoukou. I often record what she says, so I can listen to her words when I have free time. Eh? Is that weird?
303090.login: You're finally back... Commander, would you spare some time to spar with me?
303090.battle: Everyone, advance! The fortunes of war are with us!
303090.hp_warning: This is the hour of reckoning! Chaaarge!!
303090.feeling2: Commander, you wish to survey my room? That's fine... but please give me a moment to tidy up first.
303090.mission_complete: Mission complete! Commander, why don't you go check the rewards first?
303090.main: "Let your victories not be decided by the strength of your equipment, but by your abilities." That is what Myoukou taught me. |"Let those who think of the Sakura Empire also think of your name?" Hmm... Yes, that is a goal that I indeed have been working towards. |Commander, thank you for training with me every day. I'll continue to refine myself!
303090.feeling5: Sorry, Commander... when you weren't here, I started feeling uneasy and... before I knew it, I had already folded a hundred paper cranes... Um, that's weird, isn't it...
303090.upgrade: Yes! With this, I'm full of energy!
303090.unlock: Ashigara, reporting for duty. Commander, my blade shall cut down all your enemies.
303090.feeling4: Commander, what's the special occasion? You even brought my toiletry and wash towel to my bedside today... woooahh! It's already this late? I completely overslept!
303090.feeling1: Commander, if I am a nuisance to you, please let me know...
303090.propose: Commander, sneak attacks are against the rules... There's no one else around, right? Th-then... maybe it's okay to cling a little bit. Commander, you're so warm...
303090.drop_descrip: Myoukou-class heavy cruiser number three - Ashigara
303090.profile: I am Ashigara, third ship of the Myoukou-class heavy cruisers. I had the privilege and glory of representing the Sakura Empire in the Royals' Coronation Fleet Review. My habitability? W-well... some things must be sacrificed in order to survive on the battlefield.
303090.touch2: Ack...! U-um... I need to ask Myoukou about what I should do in this situation...
303090.mission: There are still a lot of missions left... Commander, I don't quite understand how to do some of these. I hope I'm not dragging you down...
303090.home: Commander, it's fine to rest every now and then, but please don't go overboard with it.
303090.expedition: Commander, the commission fleet has returned.
couple_encourage: Myoukou, we finally get to fight together!
303090.mail: The postman has already finished their job. Commander, why don't you go take a look?
303090.feeling3: U-um.. I'm not very dexterous, but I'd like you to have this origami crane that I made... though I'm not sure you can really call it a crane. I've always wanted to do something like this...

206032.detail: B-big brother... please don't stare at Unicorn so much... Uuu...
206032.main: These are called "Spring couplets." The big sisters from the Eastern Radiance taught Unicorn how to write this, ehehe~ |"Firecrackers" seem to be a specialty of the Eastern Radiance... Ah, this one is just a prop. It won't go off... |Big brother... Has Unicorn grown a bit bigger?
206032.unlock: Big brother... this present is for you... I hope you'll like it... Eh? Just seeing me in this outfit is the best gift? Ohh~ b-big brother...!
206032.drop_descrip: Big brother... this present is for you... I hope you'll like it... Eh? Just seeing me in this outfit is the best gift? Ohh~ b-big brother...!

103069.detail: Commander, did you know? Indy is thiiiiiiis cute!
103069.main: Commander, you're not getting away anymore! Come here, I'm gonna tell you all about my special Indy mags! Today's the day that I'll fully drill Indy's appeal into your head!|I didn't miss any major battles, you say? Well... if I'd have missed any of Indy's cute moments then I'd regret it so much I'd want to cry!|...! *Gasp* My Indy Cuteness Sensor is going off! Commander, you'll have to excuse me for a bit!
103069.unlock: Nice to meet you, I'm Indianaportland! ... Hm? Who's Indy? She's my precious little sister, and my most beloved...
103069.drop_descrip: Nice to meet you, I'm Indianaportland! ... Hm? Who's Indy? She's my precious little sister, and my most beloved...

301091.detail: I made friends of these bears on my journey! I suggest you try befriend them too, Commander... Er, forsooth!
301091.touch: Would you care to harken to one of my tales of valor?
301091.login: Being fully prepared is the key to going in the right direction! Say that again? The East lies *that* way?
301091.main: I've still not found Hibiki... I really do wonder when we'll meet again.|It is thanks to my compass that I have arrived at the Northern Parliament! Huh? How long has the needle been frozen in place?!|I'm curious as to how Ikazuchi and Inazuma are faring...
301091.unlock: Is this the place called the Northern Parliament?! It is colder than I thought... Th-thank goodness I brought gear for extreme environments! Hibiki, please wait a bit longer! Your sister is coming to see you!
301091.drop_descrip: Is this the place called the Northern Parliament?! It is colder than I thought... Th-thank goodness I brought gear for extreme environments! Hibiki, please wait a bit longer! Your sister is coming to see you!
301091.touch2: Oooh, I feel myself warming up! I don't know why, though... Something about it feels strange.
301091.home: To one day find Hibiki – that is the reason I set out upon this journey!

10500041.detail: Feels nice and soft, huh? Hehee. You finally get how pretty I am, Commander? Here, I'll pose for you, so take a bunch of pictures~
10500041.login: Yaaaawn... Morning already? Gimme five more minutes... Uuunngg... I gotta sober up! I got a lot of great stuff to be pumped for today! Commander, you gotta perk up too!
10500041.headtouch: Now I got animal ears just like Fubuki! How about it? Wanna give 'em a feel~?
10500041.main: I can't just stay in my room all day...? Fine, let's go! Huuh? I can't go out like this?|I wanna do a pajama party stream with everybody! That's like the best way to get close to people, right?|Commander, you're thinking I'm twice as cute as I was before, aren't you? Hehe, it just struck you, huh? No, you're seeing clearly~|Crunchy on the outside, soft on the inside, bite sized... Man, I love fried prawntheras~!
10500041.unlock: I'm the lovely high school girl, now in her extra-pure pajamas, Natsuiro Matsuri! Hey hey, Commander, what do you think? Surprised? Don't gawk at me too much~
10500041.drop_descrip: I'm the lovely high school girl, now in her extra-pure pajamas, Natsuiro Matsuri! Hey hey, Commander, what do you think? Surprised? Don't gawk at me too much~
10500041.home: Commander, you're just in time~ Hehee, Matsuri's got a special treat for you, check it! (She's lightly patting her thigh)

702021.detail: Umm... Is it just me, or are these mockup cell bars way too strong? Dangit, I just hope Gangut comes and rescues me soon...
702021.touch: Urgh...! Don't go touching wherever you want just 'cause I can't move...!
702021.login: Ughh... Why am I here, just to suffer...?
702021.main: I have a big backlog of games to play... I'd really like to go home and work on it! Please? Please!|Something smells gooood... So what if I had snacks merely 30 minutes ago? I have a needy stomach!|Grrr... I'm on my last dang legs here... Grrrr...
702021.unlock: What kinda exercise is this?! Nobody said I'd become a dang showpiece! Come on, get this thing off me, NOW!
702021.drop_descrip: What kinda exercise is this?! Nobody said I'd become a dang showpiece! Come on, get this thing off me, *now*!
702021.mission: You have new missions! Do them, quick! Trade the rewards for food to fill my stomach!
702021.mail: You've got mail. See, I can do work even with just my torpedo boats!
702021.lose: Commander, I know I did wrong, and I'm sorry, so come on... Give me some of that fooood...!

10500051.detail: Ay am afraid to swing my swords around looking like this... so Ay shall fight with you using my will-o'-wisps!
10500051.touch: Tis a swimsuit with a cute design and feel, you say? Quite so, quite so~ More praise wouldn't be undue!
10500051.login: Ay have waited for you! The ocean floor is where our next battlefield lies!
10500051.main: Umm, Commander? Would you not stare at me so much?|Many say Ay am easily amused, but that doesn't... Pfft, ahahahahah! Commander! Don't expressly try to make me laugh like this! Hahahahah!|My appearance may have changed, but my skill in battle has not!
10500051.unlock: Be cheery, for here's Nakiri~! Ay am not used to this outfit and am a little embarrassed... But Ay am Nakiri Ayame, Hololive's virtual demon!
10500051.drop_descrip: Be cheery, for here's Nakiri~! Ay am not used to this outfit and am a little embarrassed... But Ay am Nakiri Ayame, Hololive's virtual demon!
10500051.home: Welcome back! Ay haven't merely been frolicking around. Ay was just about to commence a stream in this swimwear!

701030.detail: Heheh~ Comrade Commander, have you come to participate in my new inspired experiment?
701030.touch: Hm? Did you stumble into your own inspiration, Comrade Commander?
701030.login: Comrade Commander, you came at just the right time! I just had a flash of inspiration and came up with a new strategy! Come test it out with me!
701030.battle: Can you keep up with me? Ура!
701030.hp_warning: Looks like it's time for me to get serious!
701030.feeling2: Comrade Commander, if you want people to like you, you've gotta be an interesting person yourself! In other words, what you need is a dose of inspiration!
701030.mission_complete: Long live the rewards! Err, so, where's my share?
701030.main: Gangut...? Err, I mean, Comrade Gangut? Hmm, she kind of scares me... |My fighting spirit, just like my inspiration, is unbreakable! That's right, I'll stand back up again! |When I mess up, I make sure to apologize profusely! That way, everyone will forgive me... hopefully.
701030.feeling5: All right, I finally understand now! I've finally reached a conclusion as to why I'm always thinking about you! So here's my hypothesis: I'm in love with you! Hehe, does that sound right?
701030.unlock: Ура! How's that, what'd ya think? Huh? Where I'm from, they said you're supposed to surprise the people you're greeting! What, I'm the one being welcomed?! Sorry, I mixed something up!
701030.feeling4: Comrade Commander, I thought you were a real hardass, but turns out, you're actually quite interesting! You have quite a lot of ideas of your own... and you don't
701030.feeling1: Comrade Commander, you're really quite an insipid person. You won't score any admirers that way.
701030.propose: This means we've signed off a lifelong contract! Comrade Commander, we'll always be together from here on out! Don't worry, don't worry, I'll be gentle!
701030.profile: I'm the Project 38 destroyer, Minsk. I fought in the Great War alongside my sisters! Comrade Commander, expect great things from my inspiration... and my hard work!
701030.touch2: Eh...?! Is this revenge for something I did?!
701030.mission: Comrade Commander, wait until you hear about the latest idea I got! Hey, wait, don't run away!
701030.home: I can't control my overflowing inspiration! Even though you just came back, I can't...
701030.win_mvp: How's that? My power is surging! That's right, don't get jealous!
701030.expedition: Commission complete! Hehe, first, we have to welcome everyone back!
couple_encourage: Woah, Avrora, you're totally inspir... I mean, shining today!
701030.mail: Ah, um... Just give me a minute to come up with an explanation as to what I'm doing in this room full of mail...
701030.feeling3: Ahaha... Comrade Commander, we're already friends, right? So, uh, when they come to collect debts, could you... Hey, wait, why are you running!
701030.lose: Woah, woah, time out! I'm not ready to retreat yet! Waaah!

10500061.detail: I'm showing too much skin? Ahah~ So you were totally seduced by my charms, Commander~ I see, I see! Perceiving hidden truths is a quality of a genius, as one would expect of a genius magician such as myself!
10500061.touch: My hat is sentient! It'll move if I wiggle my eyebrows! Heheh, aren't I amazing?
10500061.login: Good morning, Commander! Feast your eyes upon my charms today as well! However~ Don't make me read any weird lines!!
10500061.main: An endless broadcast... A studio that I can't leave... That won't happen to me if I become secretary, right?!|Zzz... I'm not sleepy~ Gah! What time is it?! Nothing's happening, right?|Your stares are too conspicuous! But I understand what you're thinking! You're marvelling at how alluring I am!
10500061.unlock: Here comes Murasaki Shion, Hololive's famous virtual magician! This world will bear witness to my brilliance!
10500061.drop_descrip: Here comes Murasaki Shion, Hololive's famous virtual magician! This world will bear witness to my brilliance!
10500061.home: Welcome back, Commander! Come take a look at my expert gameplay! My game sense is unrivalled after all!

301291.detail: Commander! Why not play a round of Shipgirl Bounty Hunter? There are many nice prizes you can win!
301291.touch: Would you like a refill, Commander?
301291.login: I'm positively brimming with energy! Tonight, let us "party hard," Commander!
301291.battle: I'm truly in my element in this outfit!
301291.main: Abukuma invited me to go fishing with her! So, I'm going out to meet– Y-you think it's best if I change clothes first?|Suruga! You should try a bunny girl costume too! ...Y-you wouldn't be caught dead in one? Isn't that a little extreme, even for an aversion?!|These frills fit around my ears perfectly! Which is good, because I'd become lethargic if they were too tight...
301291.unlock: Hippity hoppity! Grab a glass and have a sippity! Whew, I must say, this outfit was tricky to get into. Still, you made an exquisite pick, Commander!
301291.drop_descrip: Hippity hoppity! Grab a glass and have a sippity! Whew, I must say, this outfit was tricky to get into. Still, you made an exquisite pick, Commander!
301291.touch2: There being no danger of skirt-flipping doesn't make this tolerable behavior!
301291.home: Outstanding work! I will provide tonight's entertainment act! As soon as I come up with something entertaining... Hmm...
301291.win_mvp: I'm the fastest, strongest destroyer... And that's a fact!

10500071.detail: You think I've gotten a little sexier? Hey! My eyes are up here...! But if you're happy then I guess it's fine... Just don't always be looking so naughty.
10500071.login: Good Miorning, Commander! C'mon, let's go-go-go to the ocean!
10500071.battle: Commencing battle! Cool yourselves with this: Water Gun Splaaaasshhh!
10500071.main: Pretty cute swim ring, huh~! It's got wolf ears on the side~ what? You can't tell?|The beach is all about cold sodas and barbecues~♪ I can't wait to eat some with you, Commander. Come on, Commander!|I really like just floating on the water in this thing. Hey Commander, come try it with me~
10500071.feeling5: All right, I have the mic now... How about this song? That summer I had with you~♪ Feels like a distant dream~♪ I hope it stays summer forever.
10500071.unlock: I changed into my swimsuit, but I wonder if it looks right on me? An outfit like this might make you feel breezier just by looking at it~
10500071.drop_descrip: I changed into my swimsuit, but I wonder if it looks right on me? An outfit like this might make you feel breezier just by looking at it~

107035.detail: This is my special present just for you, Commander! Here~ ...This isn't the setup for a prank, I promise!
107035.touch: Wearing this winter outfit lets me blend into crowds! For, well, multiple reasons...
107035.login: You're so late, Commander! ...Not really, just kidding! Anyhoo, lead the way and I'll follow!
107035.main: Commander! You can borrow my mittens if your hands get cold!|Do you think Santa Claus is real, Commander? Me, I think he does, at least as someone who brings joy to people even without ever being seen!|The whole city has been swept up in the holiday mood! Isn't Christmas just the best~?
107035.feeling5: Hey, just a sec! You forgot one last present, Commander! Look over there for a minute and just... *kiss* There! Now you've gotten all of Sara's presents~
107035.unlock: Merry Christmas! Here comes Christmas Sara, shining like a star in the silent night! Hehehe, how's that for a holiday greeting? So, have you decided where we're gonna spend our Christmas Eve yet?
107035.drop_descrip: Merry Christmas! Here comes Christmas Sara, shining like a star in the silent night! Hehehe, how's that for a holiday greeting? So, have you decided where we're gonna spend our Christmas Eve yet?

605050.detail: Leonardo da Vinci... had that tragedy not occurred, she surely would've fought to the last breath for the glory of the Sardegna Empire, just like Cesare.
605050.touch: Allow me to say this: judging people by their appearance will be your downfall.
605050.login: Save your breath. Let's begin today's work.
605050.battle: It is time to clad yourselves in courage and wisdom!
605050.feeling2: As one of Sardegna's veterans, I have ample experience ranging from communication to fleet management. If you need any advice, feel free to ask me.
605050.mission_complete: One more name off my list... Oh, I was talking about the list of unfinished missions.
605050.main: A gown? I have no interest in things like that. Nor will I ever. |Commander, if I ever get invited to one of those Royal tea parties, please tell them that I am too busy with secretary work. |Some people used to hold me to lofty expectations, but it feels natural to see the next generation surpass me.
605050.feeling5: I said "let's look ahead," right? In that case, I'll cover your back. That way, no matter what happens, you can always keep your eyes ahead of you and leave the rest to me.
605050.unlock: I am the dreadnought, Conte di Cavour. There is much that I can do for you, Commander, but that depends on whether or not you are trustworthy.
605050.feeling4: Long live the glory of the Sardegna Empire... Forget it, it's all in the past now. I'm getting used to being in this fleet, so let's look ahead.
605050.feeling1: You will eventually pay the price for your arrogance.
605050.propose: You're giving such an important thing to me...? I... this is... ahh! I'm sorry, I can't keep my composure, but I'll try my best to say it... "I do!" How's that? P-please let this embarrassing ritual be over already...
605050.drop_descrip: Conte di Cavour-class battleship – Conte di Cavour.
605050.skill: This volley... shall not be my last!
605050.profile: I witnessed the ascendancy of the Imperial Fleet as well as its decay into powerlessness. Commander, I pray that you, as the leader of the fleet, will never repeat the tragedies of the past.
605050.touch2: Just how little do you think of me?
605050.mission: Hmm... The number of missions you've completed seems to be lower than the number of missions you were given. Commander, may I ask why?
605050.home: A hard fought battle. Next, there are many missions that you must attend to... Oh my, it would appear that I've accidentally finished everything. Do have some tea and rest for a while.
605050.win_mvp: One will never tire of victory.
605050.expedition: The commission squad has returned to port. Were you sending this bunch to a parade or something?
couple_encourage: A Royal Knight, huh? I never expected to fight alongside someone like you.
Cesare, follow me!
The glory of Sardegna... yes, it used to shine brighter.
605050.mail: New mail has arrived... I'm not your butler, and you're perfectly capable of getting it yourself. Look, it's by your right hand.
605050.feeling3: Commander, what do you think about when you gaze up into the night sky? I always think back to that night... when the skies were ablaze with what looked like countless meteors.
605050.lose: Ngh... Must I also bow my head to the passage of time...?
