302019.drop_descrip: I've finally finished developing my new equipment! Since we still have time, let's go and try it out in live combat right now, Master!
302019.touch2: Augh... I'm going to smack you!
302019.home: Hehe, looks like the data collection went well this time too.
302019.win_mvp: Master, have you realized the importance of having modernized equipment?
302019.lose: Hmm... Looks like I haven't upgraded my equipment enough...

501010.detail: Commander, what would you like to know?
501010.touch: Commander... Hehe~ doing this occasionally is not all that bad.
501010.login: Wow! Today's schedule looks packed. Let's work hard today!
501010.battle: What are you all fighting for?
501010.hp_warning: Commander, concentrate and be extra careful!
501010.feeling2: Commander, we have to fight to protect the things we care about. This isn't really a question of personal preference.
501010.mission_complete: Keep up the effort, don't slack off just yet!
501010.main: Woah, this is my first time seeing a battleship! |Where did Fu Shun run off to? Would it really kill her to do as I say every now and then? |My sisters - Fu Shun, Chang Chun, and Tai Yuan - are all my pride and joy!
501010.feeling5: I'm so blessed to have met you, Commander. I've made so many friends and so many memories... Hey, Commander, once I complete my duty as one of the "Four Unbreakables," let's go travel around the world together!
501010.upgrade: Now I'll be better equipped to deal with ruffians like De Haven...
501010.unlock: Destroyer, An Shan, reporting for duty! I shall protect my sisters and you, Commander!
501010.feeling4: Commander, rest assured that wherever you go, I will be there to protect you. Huh? Isn't it obvious, you're mine after all...
501010.feeling1: Commander, it's bloomring season for the hawthorne I grew around the Bohai Gulf. Can we go back and take a look?
501010.propose: Commander, my body and soul, all of my life, belongs to you from now on. Make sure to take responsibility properly.
501010.skill: Let the protection of heaven surround the brave!
501010.profile: I am the nameship of the An Shan-class destroyers, and one of the Dragon Empery's first-generation "Four Unbreakables." As the flagship, I participated in many naval exercises, carried out surveillance, and engaged in confrontations, leaving behind lasting achievements that I can be proud of. Though I never participated in live combat, I am the destroyer with the most miles under her belt in the entire world!
501010.touch2: Hey-! My sisters are going to see us...
501010.mission: Protecting the peace isn't just about fighting - you'll have to do these missions too.
501010.home: Why don't you take a break? It's not good to be too stressed out.
501010.win_mvp: Commander, being able to help you out is the greatest!
couple_encourage: Stop running around, and stay by my side!
Remember, you can never be too careful on the battlefield.
Let's see those guts! Great! Just like that!,0
501010.mail: Commander, you have new mail. Should I unseal it for you?
501010.feeling3: Even if the day comes when I am no longer needed on the battlefield, I still want to watch over the Bohai Sea. I want to always be able to see the waters, dyed a shimmering vermillion in the sunset.
501010.lose: Everyone, regroup. We can't retreat like this!

101480.detail: Breaking stuff is easy. Making stuff is not.
101480.touch: Keep the touching to a minimum, thanks.
101480.login: You're late, Commander. I oughta build you an alarm clock that keeps ringing no matter what you do.
101480.battle: Full module calibration complete. I'm loaded and ready for battle!
101480.hp_warning: Oh, crap! That's gonna be a pain to repair!
101480.feeling2: Even minor flaws impact the quality of a product. You want high-end equipment? Make sure it's perfectly calibrated.
101480.headtouch: This hairpin? It's made from a repurposed binder clip. Is that so weird?
101480.mission_complete: Need a pen to write the mission complete papers? Here, you can borrow mine.
101480.main: Yo, Commander, you mind if I do some tinkering in here? Don't wanna disturb you, is all... All righty, I'll take that as a "yes."|Why am I wearing just one stocking? Uhh, because I forgot to put the other one on. What does it matter, anyway? Clothes are just a bother.|There's a loose screw under the bookcase... No biggie, I'll get it myself. And don't you dare try to sneak a dirty peek in while I'm doing it.
101480.feeling5: Listen, if you ever need something, just hit me up. Scratch that, uhh... You can hit me up anytime, for any reason. I just feel kinda lonely without you, you know? Ahem... Anyway!
101480.upgrade: Rigging upgrades, huh? Keep them coming, thanks.
101480.unlock: I'm Ingraham, Eagle Union destroyer. Not much else to tell you, honestly... Anyhoo, good to meet you.
101480.feeling4: Yo, Commander, I scrounged up some spare parts and made you this steel medal on my day off. C'mere, I'll attach it to your uniform... Pfft! Looks pretty good on you!
101480.feeling1: I'd love to unscrew your thick skull and have a look at what's inside.
101480.propose: Here I thought you were dense, but I guess I was wrong. Oh yeah, I made this ring for you. It's no promise ring, but I still want you to have it... This thing's special to me, so don't even think about having me remake it for you.
101480.drop_descrip: Allen M. Sumner-class destroyer – Ingraham, Hull Number DD-694.
101480.profile: Thought about it some more, but I really don't have much else to tell you. On another note, wanna see the Allen M. Sumner-class miniature I made? Main battery, AA guns, even depth charges, it's all there. See?
101480.touch2: This is your dirty-deeds-hand, huh? I'm gonna keep you armlocked until you say you're sorry.
101480.mission: New missions, huh? Ugh. I don't wanna get off my butt...
101480.home: My hunch was right – this thing really is a millimeter off... Oh, hey there, Commander. Just who I was looking for. Could you have a look at this?
101480.expedition: Commission complete. Any parts you don't need? Send 'em my way.
couple_encourage: Try not to get too sloppy, Allen.
That's some cutting-edge tech you've got...
Got any pro tips for me about repairing?
101480.mail: Mail, eh... I could give your mailbox a makeover, if you want.
101480.feeling3: Hey, Cooper, I finished that "morph item" you asked about... No, Allen! Stop plastering stickers all over my stuff!
101480.lose: I've gotta do thorough rigging maintenance when I get back!

302139.detail: Commander, do you have any tactics you'd like to discuss with me? If you'd like... we can also just sit down and have a chat.
302139.touch: There's nothing wrong with wanting to see me dance... I'll show you, but only if you work seriously first!
302139.login: Did you sleep well, Commander? Do you need any help with fleet administration?
302139.mission_complete: Rewards have been issued! Want to see something interesting now that we can take it easy?
302139.main: Sometimes it's hard to prove to others that what you believe is right. Commander, let's do our best together!|Every now and then, I get a bit jealous of {namecode:38} and how straightforward she is...|Even though some people may think that cautiousness is a sign of weakness, I'll be happy as long as our fleet truly understands me...
302139.upgrade: I can always work harder for the fleet!
302139.unlock: Since I've gotten used to living with you, Commander, I've decided to be more laid-back after receiving my remodel. My dance? Hehe... I can't show that to just anyone so easily.
302139.drop_descrip: Since I've gotten used to living with you, Commander, I've decided to be more laid-back after receiving my remodel. My dance? Hehe... I can't show that to just anyone so easily.
302139.touch2: Commander, please do not mistake my cautiousness for tolerance.
302139.win_mvp: I only gave the orders, the real credit goes to the fleet!

103132.detail: Hey, Commander, make good use of your day off and give skateboarding a try. Hahah, let's start with something simple, all right? I'll keep a close eye on you, like I do when hunting prey.
103132.touch: Try and keep up if you can! Hahaha!
103132.login: Hang on, don't move! All right, hahah. Managed to grind to a halt.
103132.main: Did a Meowfficer on a skateboard just swoosh past me...? Must've imagined it...|Check out my boardslide! Haha!|Nothing beats this feeling of being able to move freely and not bound by anything!
103132.unlock: Oh crap! Move outta the way, Commander! Come on, man, look out next time! You'd have gotten hurt if I'd slammed into you!
103132.drop_descrip: Oh crap! Move outta the way, Commander! Come on, man, look out next time! You'd have gotten hurt if I'd slammed into you!
103132.home: I taught myself how to ride a skateboard. It was a piece of cake. Fitness comes with being a hunter like me.

101450.detail: So Commander, do you like being the one cuddling, or the one being cuddled? Just wonderin'!
101450.touch: What's that? You cuddle with me? Go on, try it!
101450.login: You're still in dreamland, huh? Hm... *blows*... Oh, hey! So you are awake!
101450.hp_warning: Owch! I'm not outta the game yet, though!
101450.feeling2: My rigging's in tip-top condition! Counting on you to keep it that way, Commander! Hehe!
101450.mission_complete: Mission completed! ...Wait a sec, this thing says I had zero involvement in it!
101450.main: Okay, hear me out! Why don't we spruce up the office with some stickers? These here would look great on the walls and your desk!|Man, it's crazy how much Fletcher cares for her sisters. Who, me? I, uhh, prefer a hands-off approach with my sisters!|So this is what you do all day... You don't think I could become a commander too if I studied enough? Yeeeah, me neither. Heheh. Feel a little less tense now?|You just yawned, didn't you, Commander? Just be honest and admit it~
101450.feeling5: Zzz... Hmm? Commander? *yawn*... Guess I dozed off, whoops. Could you gimme a ride to the couch? ...No? Aww, why not?! We're buds, so what's the big deal? Zzz...
101450.upgrade: Sweet! Burst of energy like this make me wanna do stretches!
101450.unlock: I'm Eagle Union destroyer Allen M. Sumner! Just call me Allen! It's a pleasure, Commander! Anyway, I've heard you've got yummy food and cushy work here at this port. That true?
101450.feeling4: So, you doing anything special on your next day off? No? Perfect! Then mark that date your calendar. I'll bring the vidya and we can game all day!
101450.feeling1: Okay, okay, calm yourself and I'll indulge you with a nice, heartwarming hug.
101450.propose: One mystery remains: did I charm you, or did you charm me? Meh, don't really matter... All that's important is now we'll live happily ever after! Hehe~ I love you so much, Commander♡
101450.drop_descrip: Allen M. Sumner-class destroyer – Allen M. Sumner, Hull Number DD-692.
101450.profile: I'm Allen M. Sumner, nameship of the class that succeeded the Fletcher class. We may not be as numerous as the Fletchers, but we've got a teensy edge over 'em in firepower and AA! Hell, I think it's no exaggeration to say we were the Eagle Union's strongest destroyers back in the war!
101450.touch2: Hahaahh! Too slippery for you! Can't catch me!
101450.mission: Beep boop, this is an automated deadpan mission reminder. Uncompleted missions detected. Do your job. Beep boop.
101450.home: Whoa! Hel-looo! The couch is all yours if you want it.
101450.win_mvp: Easy-breezy! That's another star on my record!
101450.expedition: Commission completezo! Check it out, I categorized the rewards with some stickers!
couple_encourage: Hey look, Black Cats! Pfft! Just messing with you~
Is that you, sis? Never mind, wrong Laffey!
Oh man, those new stickers you've got? They're so cute!
If it ain't the ghost that popularized oversized sleeves!
101450.mail: New mail's come in! Gonna read it later? Gotcha, I'll put a sticker on it then.
101450.feeling3: I've finished all my combat drills, so I'm gonna use my break time to run down to the store! Oh, before I forget, here's a special sticker for you! It's all good if you wanna trade it with someone later.
101450.lose: Oh crap, I really whiffed this one... Thank god for that near miss back there... Umm, I'll do better next time.

103070.detail: What are you looking at? My skin color has always been light brown, it's not a tan.
103070.login: ...?! When did you get here, Commander? You startled me...
103070.battle: I'm the captain... Wait, I'm the captain?!
103070.feeling2: ... I just have a slow reaction time, that's all, Commander. You don't need to poke me, I'm listening.
103070.main: If I go away, I guess you'll have to rely on New Mexico.|I wonder why my sister's always looking at me...|To be honest... I can't really have a proper conversation with other people...
103070.feeling5: I'm... not as cheerful as my sister, nor do I look as good as her, yet you still chose me... That makes me a little... no... it makes me very happy...
103070.upgrade: ... I feel the... power surging through me.
103070.unlock: Yeah? ... Commander, I'm Indianapolis. My nickname is Indy. Hm? A nuclear bomb? What's that?
103070.feeling4: My sister gives me everything I need, so I'll give her everything she needs, too. Except for you, Commander...
103070.feeling1: ... (It's not clear whether Indianapolis hasn't become aware of you yet or if she simply doesn't care about you.)
103070.propose: I'm really happy... but I don't know what I should say... So can I just... give you a hug?
103070.drop_descrip: Portland-class Heavy Cruiser – Indianapolis, Hull Number CA-35!
103070.profile: ... I'm Indianapolis, second ship of the Portland-class. I apologize for any trouble my big sister caused... A nuclear bomb? I'm not sure what that is.
103070.expedition: ... I almost forgot to report it, but... a commission's been completed.
couple_encourage: Shut up, Portland...
... I just have a slow reaction time...
... We are the Monkey Corps!
103070.feeling3: My sister's... always talking about how cute I am, but if she'd just focus a little more on herself, I'm sure she'd be popular... That's why I've always felt a little guilty about her...
103070.lose: ... Something feels wrong... must be that damn I-58.

207041.detail: Do you need advice from the beautiful Victorious? Whether it's fashion tips or relationship trouble, you can ask me anything~!
207041.touch: This outfit is surprisingly warm... Even in this kind of weather, I don't feel cold at all!
207041.login: Way! Too! Slow! Commander, what does your schedule look like today? Hurry up and finish so you can take me shopping!
207041.battle: Since you messed up the day off I was so looking forward to, I'm going to have to punish you!
207041.main: Rest is for the sake of being able to work better! Therefore, set aside that work and come play with me~! |Tirpitz, come and play with me~ I won't do anything to you~! |Stay in tip-top condition so you can work hard and play hard! That's my motto~!
207041.unlock: Hum~ dee dum♪~ I'm all dressed up, and my hair is perfect! Commander, I'm ready to go! Don't keep me waiting on a holiday!
207041.drop_descrip: Hum~ dee dum♪~ I'm all dressed up, and my hair is perfect! Commander, I'm ready to go! Don't keep me waiting on a holiday!
207041.home: Phew, is the battle finally over? As I said, let's go out and have some fun!

301643.detail: It's nice wearin' a cute dress 'n minglin' with a bunch of cuties~ I don't mind you oglin' me if ya want, Commander.
301643.touch: My hair ornament's slid out of place? Aw, thanks, Commander~
301643.login: Are ya fixin' for some tea, Commander? Then have some brewed usin' tea leaves I got from Yat Sen~
301643.main: Ain't family get-togethers a tradition 'round this time of year? I'll call over my sisters for a little tea time... No wait, we'll have tangyuan instead! Wanna join us, Commander?|Kasumi, how's about joinin' us for a night out? You can bring Foo and yer friends too, if ya want~|If everyone's happy, then I'm happy too~ You feelin' happy, Commander?
301643.unlock: Should I hang this "fortune" poster here...? Oh, Commander, did ya also want a Spring Festival present from Ooshio here? Just kiddin'~ Hehe, anyway, happy Lunar New Year~
301643.drop_descrip: Should I hang this "fortune" poster here...? Oh, Commander, did ya also want a Spring Festival present from Ooshio here? Just kiddin'~ Hehe, anyway, happy Lunar New Year~
301643.touch2: Commander, this ain't the place or place for lewdin', all right~?
301643.home: Go on, spend some time with all the cuties 'n have a relaxin' holiday!

101481.detail: Your job's simple. All you need to do is drink what I serve you and give feedback on the taste, mouthfeel, et cetera.
101481.login: You're on time for once! That means you're due for a reward. I'll make your drink doubly sweet.
101481.main: All I asked Allen for was some label paper, and instead she dumped a billion different stickers on me...|No, Cooper, that stuff's got alcohol in it. Put it back where you found it.|Yeah, Allen made me wear this getup when she found out I'll be handling the bar counter... That said, I guess I don't really mind it.
101481.unlock: Hmm... Could use a little more sweetness, and a splash of the secret ingredient... Oh, you're here? Great. I appoint you as my first dedicated taste-tester, Commander. We're gonna come up with some novel and fresh drinks, you and I!
101481.drop_descrip: Hmm... Could use a little more sweetness, and a splash of the secret ingredient... Oh, you're here? Great. I appoint you as my first dedicated taste-tester, Commander. We're gonna come up with some novel and fresh drinks, you and I!
101481.touch2: Hey! Wow... Hope you like your lemonade with 30 times more lemon juice.
101481.home: Once I've perfected this recipe, I'll give you a gold taste-tester medal for your efforts.
101481.expedition: Commission complete. Let's see if they brought back anything I can use...

302071.detail: When I'm wearing these clothes, I feel like I'm going to be exorcised... What do you think about them, Commander?
302071.main: A succubus is a being that tempts people in their dreams... I-I'd never do anything like that!|Isuzu, it's me, Yura! I'm not a ghost, you don't need to be afraid of me!|I don't know if today is a day of celebration, but everyone seems to be more lively than usual. I wonder if the Commander will be all right dealing with them...|It seems that thou are doing well. Hehe. Commander, do you perhaps prefer my Self to me?
302071.unlock: Uh... I think these clothes are a bit too much... Commander, I... don't look out of place in these, do I...?
302071.drop_descrip: Uh... I think these clothes are a bit too much... Commander, I... don't look out of place in these, do I...?
302071.touch2: Maybe you were the real succubus all along. Hehe.
302071.home: The wings are slipping off... Is there a mirror somewhere...?

302140.detail: Commander, would you like to study together with me?
302140.touch: Hum hum~♪ Oh, sorry, am I disturbing you in the middle of work...?
302140.login: Welcome back, Commander! I'll try to be the best secretary you've ever had!
302140.battle: My sisters, please look forward to my performance in battle!
302140.hp_warning: Everyone, stay calm! Let's change our strategy!
302140.feeling2: What I do on my days off? Well, I get up and do morning training, I read for an hour, I do target practice for 2 hours, and then... Basically, I make full use of my vacation days! I have to work really hard to become stronger, you know?
302140.mission_complete: You've cleared another mission! You're so brilliant, Commander! I'll need to work just as hard!
302140.main: If it looks like there's nothing for me to do, would you mind if I did a little training on my own? I won't get in the way of your work!|Jintsuu is wise, Sendai is strong... but I'll work my way towards both brains and brawn! ...Ahahah, though I'm not sure if I can actually do it.|If you're tired, would you like me to give you a good relaxation tip? I actually know quite a lot about it~
302140.feeling5: Huh? Are you saying you've been waiting for a chance to go on a date too? Heheh, in that case~ Why don't we do it, Commander?
302140.upgrade: With your support I can work even harder!
302140.unlock: Nice to meet you, Commander! I'm the light cruiser Naka! My sisters are better known than me, but I swear that one day I'll be even more famous than them!
302140.feeling4: Hmm, I feel a little guilty over always making you come with me... Is there anything you'd like to do? We'll do it together, of course!
302140.feeling1: My sisters chose you because you just let them mess around without being scolded? How strange...
302140.propose: You can stare as much as you'd like. Hehehe~ From now on I will use my brains and brawn to serve you, my sweetheart whom I love so much!
302140.drop_descrip: Sendai-class light cruiser number three – Naka.
302140.profile: I'm Naka, Sendai-class light cruiser number three! Due to certain circumstances, my construction was delayed, I was redeployed to place after place, and my service record as the flagship of Desron 4 isn't much to brag about... but that's okay! I'll still work my butt off to try to surpass my sisters!
302140.touch2: Eek! ...Please, Commander, try to stay focused on your work while in the office!
302140.mission: I reorganized the mission list for you! Here, please choose one!
302140.home: There's nothing better than getting to come back home. Wouldn't you agree, Commander?
302140.win_mvp: Compared to my goal of surpassing my sisters, this is no big deal at all!
302140.expedition: I think a commission has been completed. We should go and say thanks to the returning team!
couple_encourage: I want to shine as gloriously as you, my sisters!
302140.mail: Commander, I have mail for you. I picked it up on the way back from my training.
302140.feeling3: What are my hobbies? ...I don't really have one in particular. But I enjoy reading and training... Oh, would you like to train together with me? Heheheh~
302140.lose: Oh no! Commander, we should retreat immediately! Jintsuu said we shouldn't make meaningless sacrifices!

401281.detail: Should I make offerings at the shrine first, or play hanetsuki with my friends...? Ugh, there are just so many things I want to do!
401281.touch: All tuckered out from playing? Let's take a break then! I'll wake you up if there's an exciting event going on!
401281.login: Hello, Commander. I thought you were still hiding inside the kotatsu. Ehehe~
401281.main: Commander, look at this lifelike tail! Doesn't this make me look like one of those girls from the Sakura Empire?|Hmm, why does this lion have a scary face? ...Wouldn't it be better if he's cute...?|Commander, want to try some New Year dango? ...Here, open your mouth, say ahhn~
401281.unlock: Commander, Happy New Year! Is there anything you'd like to do on New Year's Day? Say, why don't we try doing all of that stuff, all at once~?
401281.drop_descrip: Commander, Happy New Year! Is there anything you'd like to do on New Year's Day? Say, why don't we try doing all of that stuff, all at once~?
401281.touch2: Promise me you won't do this any more, okay?
401281.home: I'm going to give this daruma doll a cuter expression! Um... the brush... where'd the brush go...

107034.detail: I spent a lot of time learning things about the sea! If you have a marine-related question, just ask, Commander! Professor Sara can teach you anything! Ehehe♪
107034.login: Whoosh! Ehehe~ Did you like our passionate welcoming fanfare?
107034.battle: Sister Sara won't forgive those who would destroy the peace of the seas! Go forth~!
107034.main: It feels great to pet these cuties! Don't you wanna give it a try as well, Commander?|The sea is colored navy blue, and in this moment, Sara is a true marine idol! Heheh♪|Oh yeah, I saw a seal while on patrol the other day! You should come see it with me next time, Commander!
107034.unlock: Friends of the blue sea and sky, your guardian angel and idol Sara has arrived! Ehehe~ Commander, join me in protecting the beauty of the blue seas!
107034.drop_descrip: Friends of the blue sea and sky, your guardian angel and idol Sara has arrived! Ehehe~ Commander, join me in protecting the beauty of the blue seas!
107034.touch2: Waaah?! ... Heh, hehehe... You just gave me a great excuse to test out my new gear...

402049.detail: Fishy looks a bit intimidating, but he's really kind! ... Well... I might be the only one he's kind to... Sorry...
402049.touch: Unghh... Get a grip, me! I can't faint now...!
402049.login: Phew... Commander, I, I organized your files!
402049.battle: I'm pretty nervous... but I'll do my best!
402049.mission_complete: Commander, Fishy brought us the mission rewards. Thank you, Fishy~
402049.main: You're right, a nutritious diet is important... Do you have any... um, yummy recommendations...?|Despite how Fishy looks, he really does have his own thoughts and feelings. But it seems I'm the only person who understands what he says...|It's okay, Fishy. Commander is just a little busy right now...
402049.unlock: I feel like Fishy is a lot more capable than before, but I don't feel much different... M-maybe Fishy was the one to get a retrofit instead of me?!
402049.drop_descrip: I feel like Fishy is a lot more capable than before, but I don't feel much different... M-maybe Fishy was the one to get a retrofit instead of me?!
402049.touch2: Eek! I-I managed to not faint...! Thank you, Commander!
402049.mission: C-Commander...! Commandeeeer! Don't forget your missions!
402049.expedition: Commander, would you mind if I took Fishy with us on a walk to the harbor? The commission team returned, and I want to go greet them.
402049.lose: I'm so sorry, Commander... I-I'll try harder next time!

904011.detail: Everyone looks like they're having so much fun... I couldn't ask for anything more.
904011.touch: Want to try gazing into the ocean horizon together? It always puts my mind at ease.
904011.login: Commander, are you done changing into your swimwear~?
904011.battle: Enemies...? Way to spoil the scenery...
904011.main: Ice-cream based desserts are delicious, but they melt too easily... I might have to bring a cooler with me next time...|It's been a long time since I last was able to enjoy scenery like this without any worries...|Commander, are you done changing? The others are calling for us, let's go play with them!
904011.unlock: I've been waiting so long for summer... and it's so worth it - the sun, the sand, the waves, and everyone's laughter. Commander, why don't we take this opportunity to enjoy some crullers together?
904011.drop_descrip: I've been waiting so long for summer... and it's so worth it - the sun, the sand, the waves, and everyone's laughter. Commander, why don't we take this opportunity to enjoy some crullers together?
904011.home: Commander, would you like some ice cream? I brought several different flavors of syrup.
904011.win_mvp: Who wants to have some crullers? I made more than enough for everyone~

301590.detail: O you mean this family emblem? I designed this myself, plus the clothes. I won’t accept any other comments except for “its cute”.
301590.touch: Don’t poke me unstoppingly, are you a monkey?
301590.login: So slow, are you like a turtle who’s stumbled onto the battlefield?
301590.feeling2: My fan? Its military issue, not some ordinary fan. It’s used by Admirals, so don’t underestimate me… hehehe. Hmm? I said nothing.
301590.mission_complete: The mission rewards have been confirmed, I’ll leave the labor work of transporting it here to you.
301590.main: That {namecode:128} girl, as my little sister she always acts superior to {namecode:127}, even more than I do, darn… | If only we discovered Tusk, then {namecode:70}-sama would not… sigh, forget it, what’s important is the present |Official documents? Let me see… hmm… ahh I see I see...
301590.feeling5: What, I just asked offhandedly, you sure are opinionated… forget it. I’ll still listen to what you got to say. Just you wait, one day I’ll impress you.
301590.upgrade: Thank you… my ears are twitching? Impossible, I’m not that happy at all.
301590.unlock: So it turns out to be you, are you the Commander of the 17th Destroyer fleet from today onwards? You seem so ordinary. I am {namecode:19} class {namecode:142}, show me what you got, Commander.
301590.feeling4: Actually, even though I don’t care that much and I have confidence in myself, for the sake of asking… do you think I’m independent enough?
301590.feeling1: Stay away from me, stupidity is contagious.
301590.propose: Commander, you’ve finally realized my greatness. To be frank… my ears are not twitching. I’m not that happy, shut up, let’s continue the ceremony!
301590.profile: The 17th Destroyer fleet have been together for most of the time, and we participated in all sorts of sorties and operations for almost the entirety of the war. In the end I was with {namecode:70}-sama as we both made our last stand… to the end. So I don’t care about those little things.
301590.touch2: This type of things should not be tolerated, right? In that case, die...
301590.mission: I’ve organized all the missions… say what, you want me to clear them as well?!
301590.home: You’ve worked hard today, please get some rest.
301590.win_mvp: We won… naturally, what’s there to gloat about?
301590.expedition: The commission fleet has returned, did you forget?
couple_encourage: 17th Destroyer fleet ready to take out the enemy!!
301590.mail: You’ve got mail… hmm? You read it, I didn’t really focus on what was written, don’t mind me.
301590.feeling3: {namecode:128} and {namecode:127} are both so whimsical and wandering around. Those girls sure don’t have the temperment of being in the Navy. They still need to lean on me, being their big sister. Such a headache...
301590.lose: Damn, give me… victory. Win or lose, that’s the way of life in the Navy.

904012.detail: What's your favorite dessert? I can make it for you, Commander.
904012.touch: Just relax, Commander, we still have plenty of time.
904012.login: Here you are, Commander. Oh? Don't worry, I've only just arrived myself.
904012.mission_complete: Commander, some mission rewards are available. Shall we head back to the office?
904012.main: ......der, Commander! Look at you, staring at me and spacing out again, am I really so captivating? Did the ice in your drink melt?|Commander, shall we go for a stroll? How often do we get to go out on a date? Let's not waste this one sitting around chatting.|When I sit here like this, I sometimes forget I'm a warship... But, to fight for these little moments, that's not such a bad motivation, is it, Commander?
904012.feeling5: The warm sunlight, the peaceful atmosphere, the soothing music, all embracing me as I relax and chat with one so dear to me. If this is a dream, I hope to never wake up...
904012.unlock: Don't you simply adore the atmosphere in this place? It's one of my favorites. The desserts here are to die for. Would you like a taste?
904012.drop_descrip: Don't you simply adore the atmosphere in this place? It's one of my favorites. The desserts here are to die for. Would you like a taste?
904012.mission: Is it a very important mission? Well then, I'll go with you.
904012.home: No need to rush, Commander, I don't mind waiting for you.
904012.expedition: Commander, the commission is complete... Hehe, no matter the time or place, I suppose I'm still your secretary ship.
904012.mail: We have new intelligence? Well, don't worry about me. Please, check it at once.

499020.detail: My child, if you desire absolute victory, you must maintain absolute rationality.
499020.touch: If you are ever afraid, come hide behind my back.
499020.login: The performers can wait no longer! Hurry, let us raise the curtains of battle!
499020.battle: Let us play a requiem! Resound, o hatred, fear, and despair—!
499020.feeling2: I never should have come to exist in this world... But since I am here, there must be a higher principle behind it...
499020.mission_complete: Now then, what kind of reward would you like?
499020.main: All those emotions that you’ve bottled up through all those conflicts... Listen to my concert, and let it all out. |My appearance upon the battlefield gives off an air of cruelty? Hehe... I’ll take that as a compliment. |Even should you anger me, I’ll forgive you as long as you properly apologize.
499020.feeling5: Please dote upon me more. Yes, more... more...!
499020.upgrade: I feel as if I can bring out even more beautiful music.
499020.unlock: You've returned to my side once more, my child. Tell me, what is it that you wish for? Wealth? Glory? Or perhaps eternal youth?
499020.feeling4: I do prefer this to fighting. Here, my child. Open your mouth~ ahhn~
499020.feeling1: I wonder if you’re properly repenting yet...?
499020.propose: From now on, I shall share everything with you - your sorrow, your joy, your pain, and your pleasure. My child, I will always, always welcome you into my embrace...
499020.profile: I am Friedrich der Große, prototype H-class battleship of the Iron Blood Navy. Come, my child... If you are unable to sleep, allow me to play you a lullaby.
499020.touch2: Just like a baby... how sweet.
499020.mission: My child, no matter what it is that you desire, I can help you obtain it.
499020.home: Welcome back. Whether it’s good news or bad news, I’d be glad to hear you out.
499020.win_mvp: What a pity. The encore had only just begun...
499020.expedition: We must properly praise the girls who have returned from their commissions.
couple_encourage: You should let me pamper you once in a while.
Perhaps you're unable to display your full power with me in charge?
499020.mail: Shall I sing the contents of this message for you?
499020.feeling3: Things such as courage have no value on the battlefield. Only those who approach Laplace’s demon shall approach victory.

302141.detail: I heard that surfing is a great way to sharpen your motor skills, especially your sense of balance! C'mon, let's give it a try!
302141.touch: Hehe, Commander~ Did you just offer to give me a massage~?
302141.login: We've gotta warm up before hitting the waves! C'mon, Commander, don't keep me waiting!
302141.main: Sendai, how'd you split that watermelon blindfolded...?! Th-that was so cool...! |I'm sure Jintsuu will be writing some report like "The Status of the Waves and Water in this Sea Region" after our vacation is over. Hahaha! |It sure feels nice to just float around and let the waves sweep you away~
302141.feeling5: Surfing is pretty fun once you get the hang of it, right? What do you think, Commander? Wanna go on a surf date with me?
302141.unlock: Ahaha! Another big one's coming~! Phew~ that felt amazing~! Ah, Commander, let's hit the waves together, shall we?
302141.drop_descrip: Ahaha! Another big one's coming~! Phew~ that felt amazing~! Ah, Commander, let's hit the waves together, shall we?
302141.touch2: Commander... if you do this kind of stuff on the beach, all the girls will hate you, you know?
302141.mission: Eh? Jintsuu, you even brought the mission documents along?
302141.home: There's no way to keep this tail from getting in the way when I'm swimming, huh... Wait! I'm sure Sendai knows a way around it!
302141.mail: C-Commander?! We just got a message in a bottle!

401240.detail: A mortal that does not tremble before my visage? How strange... I thought I did my best to look absolutely hellish... I wonder why...
401240.touch: These massive claws suit my status as an Archfiend, both in terms of appearance and destructive power! Ahahaha!
401240.login: Do you have any idea what time it is? This is why I can't stand you lazy mortals... Get back to work already!
401240.battle: Let us begin the festival of blood and iron!
401240.feeling2: Hrmm... Those planes circling overhead are like flies... annoying and won't go away... Don't you agree?
401240.headtouch: Impudent mortal, how dare you wantonly touch my head... W-wait, don't stop, please~
401240.mission_complete: The time of reaping seems to have come once more. Isn't that right, human~?
401240.main: Black is the mark of my infernal nobility— yes, black coffee, dark chocolate, and black forest cake... are all things within my domain! Surely even human scum such as you recognizes this~♪|Aaaahhhhh... I'm sooooo booooored... Shall I teach the next person who walks through these doors the meaning of true fear? ...No good? Tsk... |The ways of the mortal realm have no bearing upon me! Therefore, Zed, I have no need for this "homework" stuff. Oww! F-fine, I get it, so stop chewing me out!|You... forgot to bring the offerings? ...Looks like I will have to teach you about the fragility of human life.
401240.feeling5: Now that you've learned to fear and respect me, mortal, I shall give you the privilege of forming a physical pact with me! Come! ......Hug! It's a hug! Do I have to spell it for you, you fool?!
401240.upgrade: Not bad, human scum! My power grows ever greater!
401240.unlock: Tremble, mortal! Before you is the Fiend of the Crimson Darkness, the Avatar of Fear, the Iron Blood destroyer, Z24! All you need to do is grovel at my feet!
401240.feeling4: Are you offering this black forest cake to me? Ehe... Ehehehe... Very well, human. Here, ahhhn... What are you spacing out for? Hurry up and feed me already!
401240.feeling1: Do you know the fate of mortals who have fallen to such depths of depravity?
401240.propose: You seek to form a contract with me, mortal? Ehehehe... very well! I shall reward you for your bravery! From now on, you shall serve me!
401240.profile: After Z23, the 1936-class destroyers no longer were given actual names... Why?! Why can't I have a cool and easy-to-remember name like Lebe or Thiele...?!
401240.touch2: Surely you already know the fate of those who dare to disrespect me? Foolish mortal...
401240.mission: Missions? Hurry up and get those unsightly things out of my sight, mortal.
401240.home: It's about damn time, human. Tired, so I'm gonna rest. Don't bother me unless it's urgent, or you have dark chocolate.
401240.win_mvp: Ahahahaha! Fresh blood and steel, blossom into magnificent fireworks!
401240.expedition: Commission rewards? I have no interest in mortal trinkets... But oh! If there's any black chocolate or black forest cake, you must bring it to me, mortal!
couple_encourage: Let's tear them to shreds!
I look forward to seeing your dark arts!
You will no longer face the storms alone!
Devil, heed my call and destroy our enemies!
H-hey, stop lecturing me!
401240.mail: Insight from the Abyss itself... Guhuhu...
401240.feeling3: Nothing in existence can stand before me without succumbing to abject terror... or so I thought. Why aren't you afraid of me!
401240.lose: *pant*... *pant*... I don't have to hold back anymore, right? I'll destroy everything... every last bit of it...!!!

407030.detail: The expression of the passage of time as the hands of a clock ticking—don't you think it's just fascinating?
407030.touch: What is it? You've still got time left until your break ends.
407030.login: Did you just get here? Heheh. Make sure you work efficiently on your duties today, as always.
407030.battle: Let me test this tactic on you.
407030.feeling2: Time is a precious commodity. State what you need me to do as concisely as possible.
407030.mission_complete: I'm glad the rewards for the missions correspond to the amount of time it took to complete them. Hehehe.
407030.main: The more precise your plan is, the less time you'll have to waste hesitating on what you need to do. Why not give it a try, Officer?|Heinrich, your documents for your training program are here. Make sure not to forget them next time.|It's so nice to see all of the tasks be completed, just as planned. Hehehe.
407030.feeling5: Officer, you'll pay me back for all of the time I've spent for you...? Interesting. Let me check the details first, hehe.
407030.upgrade: Strengthening complete. Yes, it seems as if I've spent my time wisely.
407030.unlock: It is I, the never-completed Graf Zeppelin-class "Aircraft Carrier B," otherwise known as Peter Strasser. There is much for us to do and little time to do it... No time to waste. Let's begin.
407030.feeling4: Devoting your time to one person is a waste of time. That is, unless you get something worth it in return... Don't you think so too, Officer?
407030.feeling1: Officer, you're not worth my time.
407030.propose: A ceremony to ensure the time I've spent doesn't go to waste... well, since you've said this much, I'll take your words as proof of your vow, Officer. We still haven't spent as much time and emotions on each other we want to after all, right...? Hehehe.
407030.drop_descrip: Graf Zeppelin-class aircraft carrier – Peter Strasser.
407030.profile: I am Aircraft Carrier B, one of the Graf Zeppelin-class carriers that suffered an unfortunate fate, having had my construction halted without ever getting to set sail. But... doesn't the name "Peter Strasser" have a much nicer ring to it than "Aircraft Carrier B"...?
407030.touch2: Officer, if this helps raise your efficiency, I don't consider it time wasted.
407030.mission: Here are the new missions. Instead of rushing to finish everything at once, use your time wisely and plan out your endeavors properly.
407030.home: The more complex the machine, the more time it takes to maintain it. All the more for humans. Make sure you don't forget to rest up.
407030.win_mvp: Hah! Took care of them faster than I thought.
407030.expedition: The commissions have been completed. Yes, I'll have to praise them for their efficiency considering their station as your subordinates.
couple_encourage: Before you go and destroy the world, destroy the enemy in front of you first.
Don't just rush in. ...H-hey!
Gently now. Hehehe.
Ehem... Time is not on your side.
407030.mail: Officer, there's mail for you. Make sure to check it at your earliest convenience.
407030.feeling3: Officer, the clock in your bedroom was off by two minutes. ...Oh, there's nothing for you to worry about, I've already taken care of it. You can't use the excuse that your clock is off anymore
407030.lose: Time is far better spent contemplating how to avoid being destroyed, rather than foolhardily charging into destruction again and again.

303080.detail: What is it? Do you want to be my lackey?
303080.touch: Commander, are you feeling lonely? I just happen to have more spare time than I know what to do with~
303080.login: I-I'm not training.. I'm just... being lazy and laughing at the other girls as they work up a sweat.
303080.battle: Hmph. Another bunch of blind idiots.
303080.feeling2: Commander, you're going to be unpopular forever if you don't pay attention to your appearance.
303080.mission_complete: Heheh, looks like you couldn't have done this mission without me!
303080.main: My sisters in the Fifth Fleet? I miss them a bit... err, just once in a blue moon!|Ghosts on the training ground? W-what are you, a kid? Who'd believe something like that?|Salt Lake City? I'm going to show her that Lady Luck doesn't bless the same person forever!
303080.feeling5: I can't be honest with myself... because I can't stand the thought of people seeing me work hard... except for you, Commander. No matter who I become, surely you would...
303080.upgrade: I'm even more flawless than before!
303080.unlock: I'm {namecode:64}, the first post-treaty heavy cruiser from the Sakura Empire. My design is the very definition of perfection! I'll be in your care from here on out!
303080.feeling4: Huh? Commander? What are you doing at the training area so late? You were worried about me? I-I was just taking a walk because I was bored. You heard cannon fire? Th-that was...
303080.propose: I know I have a hard time being honest with myself, but... I'll try my best to make you the happiest person in the world! I swear my name on it!
303080.drop_descrip: Second ship of the {namecode:63}-class heavy cruisers, {namecode:64}.
303080.profile: I am {namecode:64}, second ship of the {namecode:63}-class heavy cruisers. Though I said second ship, I am no "little sister". I fought my way all around the Pacific, and served as flagship multiple times. I am greatest heavy cruiser - bear witness to my elegance and power!
303080.touch2: I-idiot... you're that fascinated with me? At least tell me in advance...
303080.mission: Only an idiot would be unable to complete such an easy mission.
303080.home: Good work. However, you won't be able to catch up to me with even ten times the effort!
303080.win_mvp: Hehe, this is only normal, of course.
303080.expedition: Mmhmm. It's important to work hard! Well, unless you're me!
303080.mail: You want your mail? Only if you beg me nicely~
303080.feeling3: Hard work? Not at all. A genius like me doesn't need to work hard. I get stronger just by breathing.
303080.lose: Damn it... just what went wrong?

407010.detail: If gods truly exist in this world, let us begin our slaughter with them.
407010.login: The black goat's horn has already sounded. Quell your anxiety and wait at ease.
407010.battle: Let us begin our symphony of destruction.
407010.hp_warning: The smell of steel and blood...
407010.feeling2: Ahh, so sweet. Sweet things cannot last for long. The only thing that endures forever is ice-cold hatred.
407010.main: I prefer the high ground, because I can see everything... everything that shall be destroyed...|Easy come, easy go... Aren't things like that better off not existing in the first place? |Life is akin to playing cards with a stacked deck. Doesn't it make you want to smash the entire table?
407010.feeling5: As long as you are here, the world does not feel so insipid and detestable. Rest easy; even if the world was to become your enemy, I would happily fight by your side. As a matter of fact, I eagerly await this day.
407010.upgrade: Ah, if only strength alone was enough to determine everything.
407010.unlock: You're my Commander? I am Graf Zeppelin. Since it appears that all the conditions have been met, let the final movement begin.
407010.feeling4: I have never been one to believe in fate, but if meeting you was also predestined... Hmm... How ironic. For the gods to have given me the worst past but also the best future... what purpose does my hatred then serve?
407010.propose: Oh? Have you finally decided to make the entire world your enemy? What? You just want to be with me? Hmph, very well. Eradicating everything that stands in our way doesn't sound bad either.
407010.profile: I am Graf Zeppelin. Though this name is worth little, you may call me by it if you wish. My only desire? To end the world. I shall not ask for your help though... as you are already a part of my plans.
407010.touch2: Quite brave, aren't you? As expected of the one I chose.
407010.mission: Is the person who gave you this mission really who you want to fight for?
407010.home: All your fights, all your struggles, are nothing more than fodder for the End.
407010.win_mvp: My enemies belong in their graves.
407010.expedition: Ah, so they have returned... Just seeing those faces filled with joy...
407010.mail: Treasure the time you have to speak with your loved ones, for that time is about to draw to an end.
407010.feeling3: Does prayer really work? Will God ever respond? Nein. Gods are called as such because they are merciless.
407010.lose: Next time, I shall grant you despair even worse than death.

102140.detail: Big sis! ... Oh, it's you. Need something?
102140.touch: ... Huh? If you've no need of me, don't call for me.
102140.login: So, you're back. I'll take my leave, then. It's too crowded in here for me.
102140.hp_warning: Big sis told me... to never give up!
102140.feeling2: I don't get why my big sis chose you. But I trust her intuition.
102140.mission_complete: Rewards, eh... Guess this is part of my job. I'll go get them.
102140.main: How can I be more like Cleveland... "Smile"? ... That might not be possible...|I don't get along with anyone but my sisters. As for you, Commander... I'll try.|Commander, I'm curious: when my sister's doing secretary work, what's she like?
102140.feeling5: I don't just blindly listen to everything my big sis says. I listen because she's always right... And I finally get why she chose you. It's because you're outstanding.
102140.upgrade: I'm one step closer to my big sis...!
102140.unlock: You're a commander? You don't... look reliable. But my big sis works for you... I've no choice, then. Montpelier, reporting for duty. I don't really care whether you give me orders or not.
102140.feeling4: I used to think commanding was just about giving orders from a comfy room while sounding like a bigshot... But after seeing it for myself, now I understand. You have a tough job, Commander.
102140.feeling1: Guess my big sis can't tell good and bad people apart...
102140.propose: Big sis told me to follow my heart. Which is why I'm here: to follow my heart. Are you following yours, Commander?
102140.drop_descrip: Cleveland-class light cruiser – Montpelier, hull number CL-57.
102140.profile: Listen, the Cleveland-class were the most powerful cruisers the Eagle Union had in the war. You should show more respect for my big sis. ... Me? I was in the battles of Midway, Augusta Bay, and a few others. I guess I did okay.
102140.touch2: G-gotta put up with it... This is obviously a test of the trust I have for my big sis...!
102140.mission: Commander, we've got a mission. Time's money... get going already.
102140.home: Well done. You should get some rest.
102140.win_mvp: This is how victory feels... Not bad.
102140.expedition: A commission's done. Aren't you gonna welcome the team back?
couple_encourage: ... I won't embarrass you, big sis!
Night battles? Two can play at that game!
Let us become fine warriors who will not disappoint our sister!
102140.mail: I left your mail over here.
102140.feeling3: My big sis is... strong, cool, has a golden smile, and she could probably beat anyone in a fight... I want to be like her one day.
102140.lose: Big sis... I'm sorry... I've stained the reputation of the Knights of the Sea...

904010.detail: What should I make... Macarons, or Mont-Blanc? Oh my, Commander, you came at just the right time. Why don't you help me decide what confection to make?
904010.touch: Commander, shall we make some confections together? My home country is world-famous for our sweets, you know?
904010.login: Commander, did you get enough rest?
904010.battle: Apologies. I have no mercy to spare for my enemies.
904010.feeling2: Glad you could make it, Commander. One moment please - the dessert is ready, I just have to make tea. Today, let's unwind and chat a little.
904010.mission_complete: Hm? I see, the mission rewards are here. Commander, I'll go get them.
904010.main: There are things in this world that you might never be able to accomplish, but that is no reason to give up hope.|It's not nice to sit around idly in port, but... Strasbourg, who took my place in leading the fleet, must feel even worse about what happened... if only the Army was able to hold out a little longer... *sigh* |Ahh~ Sweets can really take a girl to heaven... C-Commander?! How long have you been here?!
904010.feeling5: True strength is not measured by our capacity to suffer in silence, but by our courage to open up to others. Commander, that's why... if you ever feel like crying, my bosom is always available for you.
904010.unlock: The day when we can all stand together has come at last... It's an honor to be here, Commander. I am Dunkerque - please allow me to become a part of this magnificent fleet.
904010.feeling4: Commander, you're quite the conversationist. Do you find me interesting to talk to? Hehe, I make sure to remember all your preferences. Sit tight for a moment, and I'll bring some cake out for you.
904010.feeling1: Ça faisait longtemps, Commander. There's no need to worry about me; I've been doing fine.
904010.propose: If I only was able to meet you in the present because of my suffering in the past, I won't say things like "I wish I had met you sooner." However, I do hope that in the future, I will always be able to find solace in your embrace. Commander, can I stay by your side forever?
904010.skill: Let's do it just like we practiced...!
904010.profile: I am Dunkerque, 1st Division of the Line of the Vichya Dominion. As you already know, there is no glory in my service history - there is no hiding this fact. However, if you are still willing to use me, I will not let you down.
904010.touch2: What am I going to do with you...
904010.mission: There's no shortage of new missions for us to get through... Hard work is important and all, but let's not overwork ourselves.
904010.home: Commander, would you like to try my freshly baked gâteau?
904010.expedition: Oh my, it looks like the commission fleet has returned. Perfect timing - I'll invite them to try my new confections.
904010.mail: Commander, I've finished sorting your mail, so don't forget to take a look.
904010.feeling3: Back then, none of us had a choice... so I don't blame the Royal Navy for what happened. Quite the contrary - if it wasn't for them, we might not be fighting together now.
904010.lose: T'en fais pas... a defeat here is not the end.

499021.detail: Mankind's ambitions know no limits. Indeed, just like these riggings of mine... they strive to expand, to become more powerful... to command more cannons, and to seize greater glory...
499021.touch: The sensation of this embrace is the warmth of human contact... Do you understand, my child?
499021.login: Aren't you cold standing over there? Come to me, my child.
499021.battle: Turn into nothingness, along with the symphony of the void!
499021.headtouch: Shouldn't I be the one doing this to you instead, my child?
499021.main: Sakura Empire's classical "gagaku" is said to elicit profound and mysterious emotions... I'm quite curious about it. |The release of repressed emotions can be both medicine and poison. The effect depends on how well you can control your state of being. |My child, could you help me with putting on this outfit?
499021.unlock: I see, so this is a "kimono" from the Sakura Empire. Exquisitely crafted, comfortable to the touch, and elegantly designed... How to wear it? ...My child, what are you talking about?
499021.drop_descrip: I see, so this is a "kimono" from the Sakura Empire. Exquisitely crafted, comfortable to the touch, and elegantly designed... How to wear it? ...My child, what are you talking about?
499021.touch2: Do you like it here, my child? Hehehe~
499021.home: Welcome back. I've prepared a beverage for you. Come warm yourself as I read the report to you.

301591.detail: You should know that I designed this outfit just by seeing the family crest here. Do you think it looks good?
301591.touch: Santa Claus? ... Hmph, I graduated from that fairy tale long ago.
301591.login: Merry Christmas. I suppose I'll let you take it easy today.
301591.main: {namecode:143}, stop frolicking around like a little kid, and don't pull on me either! Ugh... what am I going to do with you? |I still have to prepare presents for the three stooges... Jeez, can't they be a bit more considerate towards their big sis normally? Oh well, I suppose that's how it should be. |It's snowing... Hmm? It's not like I particularly want to play in the snow or anything, but if you want to so badly, I suppose I can tag along.
301591.feeling5: Look here, Christmas nowadays is a holiday that you celebrate with those who are important to you. You came here knowing that, didn't you? Me? I... don't particularly object...
301591.unlock: Before you raise a fuss about it, let me just tell you this - the concept of "Christmas" already existed during the Sengoku period, so there's nothing weird about putting on a Christmas outfit!
301591.drop_descrip: Before you raise a fuss about it, let me just tell you this - the concept of "Christmas" already existed during the Sengoku period, so there's nothing weird about putting on a Christmas outfit!
301591.mail: Another greeting card for you... Curse you, what a normie.

407032.detail: If you have nothing else to do, go read a book. Much can be learned from the experiences of people past—in essence, earning time.
407032.touch: ...Phew. (whispers) Umm, drinking beer at a party is a bit out of place, isn't it...
407032.login: I'll have you escort me tonight. Quickly now, come take my hand.
407032.battle: Come–– The time of our destruction is nigh.
407032.mission_complete: Hehe. These rewards... Well worth the time spent, right?
407032.main: The "Unhulde," you say? ...Officer, keep your eyes on me. I shan't let her steal your attention or your time.|Viersechs, Zeppelin is over there. Hehe, how cute. Don't you think so, too?|I'll bring some drinks over. ...Are you trying to show off? Go make your rounds with the others first.
407032.unlock: You already know, don't you? Since I spent so much of my precious time changing into a dress for your sake... Heh, I'll be taking plenty of your time in return. Hehehe.

102210.touch: Awright! It's my turn to be it! One, two, skip a few... Ninety-nine, a hundred! Here I come, Commander!

102210.battle: We're headed for the ocean! Chaaaaarge!!
102210.feeling2: The key to happiness is to not worry about the stuff you don't get. Isn't that right, Commander?
102210.mission_complete: Sooooo many rewards! Well? I'm pretty helpful, aren't I?
102210.main: My sisters always told me to ask if there's anything I don't understand. But, what if I still don't get it? |Hrmmm... Is there some way to get everyone to know about how awesome I am? |Ehhh? Commander, doesn't it get boring sitting there all day?

102210.feeling4: No matter what kind of stuff I ask you, you always have an answer... Commander, are you actually pretty smart?!
102210.feeling1: Don't feel bad, Commander, it's not your fault that you're dumber than San Diego.
102210.propose: What's this shiny, loopy thing? I'm supposed to put it on my finger? Ooh, it's so pretty! Hehe, I guess I'll keep it on then!
102210.skill: Got it! It's about time we get serious~!
102210.profile: I'm the third ship of the Atlanta-class light cruisers, San Diego! I'm aiming to become the fleet's number one Super☆Star!

102210.home: Commander, were you trying to play hide-and-seek with me?

Together, we're ☆invincible☆!
102210.mail: Commander, you always get so much mail... Next time, I'll write you a letter too!
102210.feeling3: What should I do if there's stuff that I can't stop worrying about though...? Ah! Got it! That's what Commander is there for!

Anyway, please let me fight to my heart's content on the battlefield!

501020.feeling3: *slaps rocket* Commander, this bad boy will take you all the way over the sky. Isn't it a beaut? I made it myself. Coming down? Don't worry about that, Chang Chun and I will be there to catch you.

305058.detail: I am able to smile from the bottom of my heart when I am here. Yes, I am very fond of this place!

103071.drop_descrip: School life... It's nice as long as you and my sister are here... I think...

502023.mail: There's so many fan letters...! Being an idol is so exhausting...

Being able to play with everyone s a lot of fun, but... I am a bit jealous of Mutsu's boundless energy.

305061.detail: Commander, both now and back during the Warring States Period, why do people fight...?
305061.touch: Hiyaaah! ... Hmm, Commander, how do I learn to look cool while swinging my sword like Takao?
305061.mission_complete: Commander, how many koku are the mission rewards worth? And what is a koku?

Let's go exploring inside it together!|Commander, Commander! Tell me more stories about the Warring States Period!
305061.unlock: Commander, check it out! "Nothing can stop me!" Urakaze made it for me! Now I can play warring states with her! Heheh, you should know I'm a force to be reckoned with! Can't you come play with us? Why not?
305061.drop_descrip: Commander, check it out! "Nothing can stop me!" Urakaze made it for me! Now I can play warring states with her! Heheh, you should know I'm a force to be reckoned with! Can't you come play with us? Why?

305061.win_mvp: Commander, when I imagine I'm an amazing general, my battles somehow get way easier! Why's that?
305061.expedition: Commander, I read in a book that having stuff is important in war! Remember to frequently claim your rewards!
305061.mail: Commander, you have new mail! Is it a report from Mitsu-what's-his-name?

108020.detail: Hohoh, I must've caught your attention~ Let me guess... you like 'em young, don't you, Commander?
108020.touch: Oh, my! Not even submarines are safe from the Commander's evil clutches!
108020.login: The Commander's back? Sweet, today's gonna be jam-packed with mischie... Err, I mean, time for work!
108020.battle: Who's it gonna be next~? Teehee♪
108020.hp_warning: Huh? Have they spotted me or something?
108020.feeling2: You wonder what'd happen if you tick me off? I'd host something like a public exhibit of your greatest blunders!
108020.mission_complete: Sweet mission rewards! So, when am I getting my share?
108020.main: So, who are you into, Commander? Come on, tell me~ It'll be a secret between us... At least for a while!|I'm SOOOOOO tireeeeed~! Lemme sit on your lap, Commander! ... Sweet! 108020.feeling5: H-hey, listen... If some day I don't come back from the battlefield, would you... Ahahaha! Like that's ever happening! C'mere! I'm gonna tickle you senseless!
108020.unlock: Tadaaah! I'm Albacore, from the Eagle Union! Oh, did I jump out and scare you? Sorry 'bout that~! I'll be a member of the fleet from now on, so let's get along!
108020.feeling4: It's mean to mess with you all the time, so today, you'll get a nice, relaxing massage! ... *Phew*... Hey, you feeling something inside your ears? It's your fault for blindly trusting me like that!
108020.propose: Just claiming my ring. If that's all then I'm gonna get going now... What? You're not gonna stop me? I-I'm telling ya, I really will walk outta here! ... Fiiiine, you win! I admit it, I just can't be without you anymore!
108020.drop_descrip: Gato-class submarine – Albacore, Hull Number SS-218.
108020.profile: My achievements? Let's see... Oh, right! I sank Taihou! She shouldn't have sunk so easily, though... Actually, why DID she sink?
108020.touch2: I wonder what'd happen to you if I were to scream for help right now... Wanna find out? Heheheh~
108020.mission: Give me a massage and I'll keep quiet about that time you slacked off~
108020.home: Weeelcome back! ... Why's the paperwork been stacked into a pyramid? Gee, a strong wind must've done it~!
108020.expedition: Commission complete! C'mon, let's go! We can't just sit here and keep 'em waiting forever!
108020.mail: You've got mail! Say "pretty please" and I'll give it to you~
108020.feeling3: My shoulders are so stiff after a long day of swimming... Oh, I have an idea! If a certain someone gives me a massage, I might just forget that really embarrassing thing they did!

408100.detail: My rigging's got bits that'll hurt ya, so watch yourself if ya wanna feel it.

408100.battle: Wanna hazard a guess where I'll appear from~?
408100.hp_warning: Oh crap! Might be time to dive back down and hide...

408100.feeling5: Sometimes I just wanna be right beside you, sometimes I just wanna hide and watch ya struggle to find me. Y'know, I think I'm in love! You made me feel this way, and you'll own up to it, won'tcha? Hehehe~
408100.upgrade: Now that's a nice boost to my swimming skills!
408100.unlock: I'm the hunter that prances across the open seas, U-37! ...Huh? Is the commander here always this spaced out? Well, I've given you my name already, so catch ya later~!
408100.feeling4: When ya go on missions in remote oceans, ya gotta live with being alone for days in a row... But I've got this photo of you in your sleep to help stave off the loneliness! Heheh~
408100.feeling1: Miss me with your lame ass! Laterrr!
408100.propose: I knew this day was comin', but I'm still feeling all giddy! Thank you for this, my lazy but adorable Commander! I'll always be with you from this day onward!
408100.drop_descrip: Iron Blood Type IXA submarine – U-37.
408100.profile: Difference between us Type IX's and the Type VII's is that we're bigger and can go farther! We hide where they'll least expect us... then BAM! Torpedo 'em to smithereens! ...The what in Hudson Bay? They just made that up for that movie! The real me was still alive and kickin'!
408100.touch2: You got a kink for submarines or somethin', Commander? Well, well...
408100.mission: New mission, huh? I'm on it! ...What? We're not disruptin' cargo lanes?
408100.home: The deep sea hunter's back, baby! Didn't score any prey, but I just caught me an slacking commander! Heheh!
408100.win_mvp: We are so throwin' a party when we get back!
408100.expedition: Commission team's back? I'll go greet 'em! Better that than be bored to death in this office!
couple_encourage: Wolfpack, let's mess 'em up!
408100.mail: Look at that, new mail! Wonder if it's from across the pond.
408100.feeling3: Check out my massive rigging, it's big enough for two people! Hop on and I'll take ya some place far away!
408100.lose: Well damn. Better luck next hunt, huh...

206052.detail: Our work takes us to the far corners of the world. Keeping a game console on hand to stave off boredom is a good idea, isn't it?
206052.login: C'mon, Commander! Which stage are we gonna clear today?
206052.main: Long Island, down to host another raid next time? I want to get some new equipment~♪|Bogue's pitches are way too overpowered... No matter how hard I try, I can only hit two or three out of ten... |Listen to this, Commander! I learned how to cook from Mullany! ...Eh, I learned the wrong thing...?
206052.unlock: Heck yeah! Another achievement down! ...Huh? Good day, Commander. Is there something wrong with my appearance? Hehe, I'm from the Eagle Union after all, of course I'd know a thing or two about entertainment~♪
206052.feeling1: Commander? It wouldn't hurt to go outside and do something else every now and then, all right?
206052.drop_descrip: Heck yeah! Another achievement down! ...Huh? Good day, Commander. Is there something wrong with my appearance? Hehe, I'm from the Eagle Union after all, of course I'd know a thing or two about entertainment~♪
206052.touch2: Jeez... games aren't enough for you?
206052.home: All right, time for me to grab that high score!

307022.detail: Commander, if you have that much free time, why don't you help me with the New Year's decorations?
307022.touch: Preparing for the New Year sure requires a lot of stuff...
307022.login: Since it's the New Year, you could probably afford to rest a little. I wouldn't mind.
307022.main: Akagi, your eyes make you seem like you're hunting for prey... |Forgetting about war and just enjoying the holidays... this isn't so bad every once in a while. |Go home, Eugen, you're drunk... Commander, come give me a hand here.
307022.unlock: One must wear appropriate attire for the New Year. What do you think, Commander? Let me hear your opinion.
307022.drop_descrip: One must wear appropriate attire for the New Year. What do you think, Commander? Let me hear your opinion.

305051.detail: Commander, what are you going to do on your next day off? I-I would not mind hearing you out.
305051.touch: Commander, did you plan to invite me out? ... Very well. Our interests happen to be in concordance.
305051.login: *yawn* Oh... Commander? I desire a few more minutes of respite... Good night...
305051.main: Good timing. I require your assistance in locating my lost clothes... Just so you know, I did not misplace them because I was playing around, understood?! |I sometimes envy Mutsu... Even though I have my freedom now, unlike when I was placed upon a pedestal and worshipped, I can't be carefree like her... |Commander, you should come visit me more often if you're not busy. Though Mutsu and Kawakaze keep me company, this place is still too spacious for my tastes.
305051.feeling5: I-I'm only doing this because... I'm prepared to entrust everything to you, Commander! ...I won't let you take back your word now! I a-absolutely will not allow it!
305051.unlock: I shall be hosting the commander today. Manjuus, I beseech you to help me look my best. I am... *yawn* a bit sleepy... Urghh... what is that ruckus out there? C-Commander! When did you arrive?
305051.drop_descrip: I shall be hosting the commander today. Manjuus, I beseech you to help me look my best. I am... *yawn* a bit sleepy... Urghh... what is that ruckus out there? C-Commander! When did you arrive?
305051.home: Commander, do you hunger? Then do partake of this dango.

102081.touch: The smartest person is the one who is the happiest! Ehehe, that's why San Diego is the smartest!
102081.main: That's strange, why's the microphone cord getting shorter and shorter? |I don't really get it, but if I work hard, it'll be A-O-K! |Commander, wanna sing a few songs as well? Ehehe, here, here! Wooaahh! (CRASH) W-who tripped me?
102081.unlock: Merry Christmas! Super idol San Diego, making her dazzling debut! Commander, you must come to my performance! ...Venue?! What's that?
102081.drop_descrip: Merry Christmas! Super idol San Diego, making her dazzling debut! Commander, you must come to my performance! ...Venue?! What's that?

107231.detail: I got this collector's edition of "Saratoga: Beautiful Summer Days" from Gridley. Looking at Saratoga enjoying the summer with everyone else makes me wish I could join her...
107231.touch: You want to get on? I-it's not that I don't want you to, but...
107231.login: Have you done your stretches yet? You don't want to get cramps because you rushed into the ocean unprepared.
107231.main: Hehehe. With this, I'll be able to improve my sense of balance and my physical strength at the same time. Would you like to give this a try as well?|...It really will be a problem if my hair gets all messy from this. Um, Commander... do you think you could tie it down for me?|Independence and the others are calling for me? ...All right, I'll go.
107231.unlock: Commander, are you also here to swim? ...Ah, this here? I brought it with me to the ocean to get some practice in.
107231.drop_descrip: Commander, are you also here to swim? ...Ah, this here? I brought it with me to the ocean to get some practice in.
107231.touch2: W-wait a second! If you move too suddenly, it'll capsize... Wah?!
107231.home: If you stay out while the sun's blazing... you're going to get heatstroke. Make sure not to let the sun cook you for too long.

305060.detail: Commander, help me inspect my third turret!
305060.login: Oh, hi, Commander! Something I don't understand happened while you were away! Why do... (Mutsu began asking a series of questions.)
305060.hp_warning: I want to protect my friends!
305060.feeling2: Ever since Nagato and I were at Hashira Island, I've wondered... Why is the sky blue? Why can birds fly? Why do we fight? ... There are so many things I wonder...
305060.mission_complete: Commander? I put the mission rewards on my turret and brought them here! But don't wake up Mr. Kitty!
305060.main: Why do we need to write like this? Is it wrong to do it this way? Why?|I saw something interesting outside! Can I go check it out?|I wonder where those ants are heading... I wanna find out!
305060.feeling5: What I wanted to ask was... umm... do you like me? Are my questions annoying? And... Oh, right! I wanted to say that I love you, and I love all the friends I've made here!
305060.upgrade: I'll give it all I've got!
305060.unlock: Hello, I'm Mutsu! Nagato's little sister! Um, are you a commander? Why? How do you become a commander? Is it cool to be one? Tell me, I wanna know!
305060.feeling4: Commander, can we play? Umm, if you've got work to do, I can come back later. I have so much to ask, and also so, sooo much I wanna tell you!
305060.propose: So this means we'll be together as one? That's amazing! It really does feel like I'm together with you when I look at this ring! Why's that?
305060.skill: Mr. Kitty, hang on tight! I'm gonna get serious!
305060.profile: I'm Mutsu, second ship of the Nagato class! Nagato and I used to swap back and forth between being the Combined Fleet's flagship! Later on, Yamato took on the role, though! Isn't it amazing how much there is to see in the world~? My third turret? Uh... I think it'll be okay this time.
305060.touch2: Commander, why are you touching me? What's the meaning behind it?
305060.mission: Commander, what's this mission about? ... What about this one?
305060.home: Hold still, Commander! I'm gonna perform an exorcism on you!
305060.win_mvp: Commander, look! I saw a really pretty fish just now! What kind of fish was it?
305060.expedition: Commander, some people just came back to the port!
couple_encourage: Nagato~! Let's give it all we've got!
305060.mail: This must be "mail"... I'll write a "mail" to you, so send me a "reply" later!
305060.feeling3: I know some things you're happier if you don't know about, but... I still want to know! Besides, aren't there lots of things you're happier if you do know about them?
305060.lose: Commander, it feels like my third turret's gonna...

603010.detail: Umm... What was I doing just now? Do you have any ideas, Commander...?
603010.touch: I've heard that hugs help people relax~ Shall we test that theory, Commander?
603010.login: Right on time~ Way to go, Commander~!
603010.battle: Come on, everyone! We are born winners!
603010.feeling2: I much prefer complimenting and congratulating people over scolding and blaming them~
603010.mission_complete: Yup, yup, mission complete! Keep it up, Commander~!
603010.main: You've already finished all the paperwork? That's great~!|Tea blends, let's see... Hmm, would any Royal girls take issue with this mix? Yeah, they might...|Looks like I'll get to enjoy both the Dragon Empery's AND the Sakura Empire's cuisine at this port~ That's wonderful~
603010.feeling5: As long as you need me, I accept you for who you are, Commander. No matter what happens, I'll always be here for you~ See? Everything's all right~
603010.upgrade: Please take good care of the others as well, okay?
603010.unlock: I am Trento, first heavy cruiser of the Sardegna Empire, here to help out. I'll support everyone in my own special little way, so please do look forward to that, Commander♪
603010.feeling4: Are you having troubles of any kind? Could you share them with me? Telling others what's on your mind can be a great help~
603010.feeling1: Don't give up, Commander! If you just make amends for your mistakes, nobody's going to abandon you!
603010.propose: I thought I was prepared for this, but now with the ring on my finger, I feel so unbelievably happy~ With all my heart, thank you, Commander. Ehehe, we'll always be with each other now, so if anything ever happens, please let me know!
603010.profile: I am the nameship of the Trento class, but if you count the days since our launches, Trieste has a longer service record. Speaking of which, I had a little incident on my launch day... but I still carried out my missions as a member of the Sardegnian fleet~
603010.touch2: That's naughty, Commander! You'll be unpopular with the girls if you keep doing stuff like this.
603010.mission: If we push on just a little more, we can take on a new mission!
603010.home: You're amazing, Commander! Bringing home another victory for the team~
603010.win_mvp: Very well done, everyone! I'm so glad we won~!
603010.expedition: The commission team is back, safe and sound. May I head out to receive them?
603010.mail: Please don't forget to check your new mail!
603010.feeling3: Please have some of this stamina-recovering coffee! ... Oh, does it taste bad? Let me try... Eww?! I might have mistook salt for sugar...
603010.lose: It's okay, it's okay! This isn't anybody's fault!

301090.detail: T-the reason I sleep with the lights on is because... i-it is not because I am afraid!
301090.login: My name is {namecode:11}, I am the ninja who will banish all the darkness in the world! ... Whoa! Commander, w-when did you get here?!
301090.feeling2: I am a little worried... about {namecode:13} and {namecode:14}...
301090.main: Sometimes I do not understand what {namecode:13} and {namecode:14} are trying to say...|Can {namecode:12} find her way here on her own? It has me somewhat worried...|W-w-what! Anyone would be shocked from suddenly seeing a person's shadow cast in the light in the middle of the night!
301090.feeling5: We Division Six destroyers have always been together! And... um, surely you will be together with me forever as well, Commander?
301090.upgrade: As the oldest of my siblings, I must work even harder!
301090.unlock: I am {namecode:11}, the oldest ship of Destroyer Division Six! Well met, Commander. I sincerely hope you will let me rebuild Division Six! ... Huh?! You do not permit the formation of destroyer divisions?!
301090.feeling4: I cannot sleep well without my sisters by my side... T-that is not to say I am lonely! I-it is because I am concerned about them!
301090.propose: A promise that binds us for eternity... I understand! Then I shall show you my true right eye, right this mo... T-there is no need for it? All I need to do is close my eyes instead? Re... really...?
301090.profile: I am {namecode:11}, a special-type destroyer! Destroyer Division Six consisted of me and my sisters! I was the first to be built and the first to be sunk! The Battle of Guadalcanal? I-I was trying to cast my light on the enemy! I was by no means scared of them! ... Ahem, you shall witness how strong I truly am... that you will!
301090.touch2: S-should you touch me there again... then I will not be able to restrain myself!
301090.mission: The ocean at night is a little scary... N-nay, I am not scared! B-but may I propose we do missions during daytime? You must agree, right?!
301090.home: Commander~ Did you bring back any shiny items? ... Hm?! N-not at all, I am not asking simply because I want such things!
301090.win_mvp: This is the true power of a ninja!
301090.expedition: We may use my searchlight to find our way home! Huh? ... You have no need of it? R-really...?
couple_encourage: Together we shall shine a light on the darkness!
We will always be together!
301090.mail: New mail for you! Uh... I will read it out loud for you!
301090.feeling3: Commander, do you perhaps wish to see my true right eye?
301090.lose: Damn... I-I shall get you next time...

605061.detail: Want me to make a training plan for you? ... "Cesare's training methods send nutrients to your muscles and away from the brain"? Did Cavour really say that?!
605061.touch: Are you out of breath already? You've still got a long way to go, Commander.
605061.login: The treadmill is free right now. Do use it if you plan to work out.
605061.main: "Inaction saps the vigor of the mind"... Who said that, again?|Jogging courses, fat-burning courses, rolling hills courses... Is it really this complicated? I'll just start with whichever seems the toughest.|If you feel stressed out, just let it all out on that sandbag over there. I can attest that it does wonders for the mood.
605061.unlock: Both exercise and war are at their core about willpower! Now, get ready, Commander! We're not finished until you're dripping with sweat!
605061.drop_descrip: Both exercise and war are at their core about willpower! Now, get ready, Commander! We're not finished until you're dripping with sweat!
605061.touch2: What was that for?! Don't ignore me, answer!
605061.home: Here, take this! Don't forget to rehydrate.

607010.detail: So this is how you're supposed to launch carrier-based planes... I think I've got the hang of it... Hyah! ...Oh no, I guess it really is nothing like launching seaplanes...
607010.touch: My Commander, did you need me for something?
