607010.login: We're going to have a busy day. Thanks in advance, my Commander.
607010.battle: Mm, hmm! Yes, this is how it's supposed to be... Fly, my aircraft, fly!
607010.hp_warning: I'm not some frail young miss who'll go down in a single blow...!
607010.feeling2: My Commander, have you already completed today's missions? And did you finish checking off the documents? This is just a friendly reminder from Aquila~ Mhm, no need to thank me~
607010.mission_complete: My Commander, I just knew you'd complete your missions without a hitch! Thank goodness~
607010.main: Sleeping on the job is not something that an excellent commander would do. My Commander... *poke* *poke*... Care to wake up?|My Commander, you should try using gentle words to get an emphatic point across. You'll find the results quite remarkable.|My Commander, will you allow me to organize the warehouse with the help of my planes? ...The previous accident? Well, that was just a one-off thing~ Ahaha...
607010.feeling5: There's been something on my mind recently... "Just how should I make myself more appealing to you, My Commander?" ...What do you think? Please, teach me all sorts of things~♪
607010.upgrade: I feel more experienced now... As long as I do as I practiced in battle, I'm sure everything will be fine!
607010.unlock: Good day to you, my Commander. I'm Aquila, aircraft carrier from the Sardegna Empire. Our meeting today is no mere coincidence. No, it must be a gift from Fortuna herself, I'm sure of it.
607010.feeling4: My Commander, look out! ...Phew, thank goodness. By the way, why did you come visit me in the middle of my aircraft training? Did you... perhaps want to see me at my most vulnerable?!
607010.feeling1: My Commander, are you still alive? ...Well, if I keep doing this, I'm sure you will come back to your senses...! *thwack*!
607010.propose: I've prepared many, many words for today's occasion, but first, I'd like to hear your words of love, my Commander~♪ After all, you're the one who proposed to me. Hehe, what do you think I should do?
607010.skill: I do believe it is time to say goodbye~
607010.profile: My "history"...? Hmm... I do feel a longing for something like that. If only I had been finished a little sooner during that war... My Commander, don't you think I would've had an enviable service history?
607010.touch2: My Commander, I do apologize, but... may I refuse this kind of behavior...?
607010.mission: We've got a mission direct from the Naval HQ... It might be pretty tough...
607010.home: My Commander, should I assist you in turning down any troublesome requests?
607010.win_mvp: Oh my, I won! Hehe, was this victory to your satisfaction, my Commander?
607010.expedition: A commission has been successfully completed! Good work, everyone! My Commander, make sure to offer them words of praise as well!
couple_encourage: I do hope we can get along, Miss Graf Zeppelin.
Well met, fair ladies of the Royal Navy~
Wow, as dashing as ever today~
Have a nice trip~ Uh... Did I get something mixed up?
607010.mail: There's new mail, my Commander. Please choose your words carefully when replying.
607010.feeling3: Miss Graf Zeppelin? In terms of our history, I'm quite similar to her, right? In that case, "I shall hope that we may forge the bonds of camaraderie"... Eheh~
607010.lose: Ugh... Did I make a mistake somewhere...?

608011.detail: I'll trade you this shell for a coconut, Commander... Hehe, hehehehe... You have only to g-gain from this deal, don't you see? Hehehe...
608011.touch: You're not p-planning something, are you...? Hehehe...
608011.login: Eep! H-how do you keep appearing out of nowhere...
608011.main: Don't be scared, little turtle... I won't hurt you, I just wanna watch... Hehe, hehehehe...|I need this straw hat to protect me, or else the sunlight would melt me...|A letter in a bottle? The ocean currents must've brought it here... Hehe, it's the plight of a poor girl who'll never be real... Hehe, hehehehe...
608011.unlock: Hehe, hehehehe... We have this little c-corner of the beach all to ourselves... Now, what should we do first... Hehehehe...
608011.drop_descrip: Hehe, hehehehe... We have this little c-corner of the beach all to ourselves... Now, what should we do first... Hehehehe...
608011.touch2: Good thing it's j-just us two here... Hehe, hehehehe...
608011.home: Back already? Hehe... I'm not alone in being a bad swimmer... Hehehehe...

102141.detail: The Sakura Empire's New Year's celebration is... a bit different from my expectations.
102141.touch: ...You'd like to see me dance in this outfit? Commander, you're as prone to flights of fancy as always.
102141.main: The sleeves on this outfit are long and heavy... and this, uh... dress? It's really hard to move around in. Don't they find this cumbersome? |If Cleve was to wear this outfit... Hmm, I can't picture it after all. |My New Year's wish...? I'd like to get a bit closer with Cleve, I suppose...
102141.feeling5: Spending the end of the year with you isn't so bad... You really still want to see me dance in this outfit? Hmm... I'm probably a bit rusty, but let's just consider it a rehearsal for when I'm doing this for Cleve.
102141.unlock: So this is Sakura-style New Year's attire... If Cleve was also interested in this... Hm? Commander, were you watching? Um, well, Happy New Year's.
102141.drop_descrip: So this is Sakura-style New Year's attire... If Cleve was also interested in this... Hm? Commander, were you watching? Um, well, Happy New Year's.
102141.touch2: Everyone is hard at work preparing for New Year's... but what in the world is going on inside that head of yours?

701050.detail: I've always been good at dancing, and I trust that my vocal skills won't disappoint either... Still worried about me, dear comrade? ...So, you're too much of a worrywart. I can handle this.
701050.touch: Chocolate for me? Is that so... Thanks for the support, dear comrade.
701050.login: Dear comrade, please go over our daily itinerary with us.
701050.battle: Ура! Let's get this show on the road!
701050.hp_warning: My dear comrade is watching me...!
701050.feeling2: Are you looking forward to my idol debut? Is that so... Well, considering this is an armament test and whatnot, I guess I can put in a little effort.
701050.headtouch: Are you seriously giving me the kiddie treatment? Hmph!
701050.mission_complete: That should wrap things up! You did pretty well!
701050.main: The other experimental ships all have instruments? Is that so? I don't plan on losing to anyone, no matter who they might be.|That Albacore really is something... She's got ideas for everything from costumes to choreography.|It's hard to keep your dance steps in sync... If you're just singing, you can pretty much hear how things are going. But if you're focused on dancing, you can't always be looking at the others.
701050.feeling5: Dear comrade, what do you think of me now? ...Is that so. Look, I've taken lessons with the others and performed on stage. You don't need to worry about me anymore, for real this time. Hehe~♪
701050.upgrade: Guess it's time to get serious. Hehe.
701050.unlock: How do you like my outfit, dear comrade? ...Is that so? After all of Tashkent's work to become an idol, that's how you react? Hmph. Just you wait. My next concert will rock your socks off.
701050.feeling4: It really is hard to express our individuality while performing as a group... Even though my dear comrade was concerned, I still... Oh, what is it? Did you come to help me...?
701050.feeling1: I can do this by myself... I don't need your help.
701050.propose: Heheh~ You're still too naive, dear comrade. There's no way I'd be satisfied with just being one star in a constellation. I'll shine the brightest of them all! That's why you shouldn't take your eyes off me even for a second~♪
701050.drop_descrip: Dear comrade, what do you think about this outfit? Is that so... I went out of my way to become an idol and that's your reaction? Hmph, I'll rock your socks off soon enough.
701050.skill: Don't even think about looking away!
701050.profile: I'm Tashkent, destroyer from the Northern Parliament, and now an idol participating in the experimental Muse System. I'll show you the tenacity of the Northern Parliament.
701050.mission: Dear comrade, there's work to do. Come on, let's get to it.
701050.home: Cola and tea, chocolate milk, juice, and vodka... Everyone's back all right... Dear comrade, what would you like?
701050.win_mvp: This victory is a testament to my abilities, not just that of the Muse System!
701050.expedition: The commission has been completed. Even if I'm an idol, I can't neglect my normal line of duty.
couple_encourage: That girl... is it even possible to dance like that?!
701050.mail: Looks like work from the agency. Dear comrade, let's look it over before showing it to Baltimore's group?
701050.feeling3: Dear comrade, are you concerned about our teamwork? Heh, there's no need for concern. This kind of cooperation is second nature to us girls from the Northern Parliament.
701050.lose: Were we out of step? But why...?

702011.detail: Roleplaying as a damsel in distress is rather new and exciting. Hehe~
702011.touch: I'm not particularly cold, you know? I'm actually pretty used to it. Commander, make sure you stay warm though.
702011.login: Ah, Commander, welcome back. Did you come to save me? Here, I'm all yours~
702011.main: This building's ambience and lighting are just right. Heehee~ |"I won't surrender myself to fate. I pray that the light of dawn will reach even this dark place."|Even if my knight in shining armor was to come, they probably wouldn't be able to get past the bears... Just kidding~♪
702011.unlock: "I am Avrora, the princess bound within this tower by a cruel fate... My beloved, please come for me soon..."
702011.drop_descrip: "I am Avrora, the princess bound within this tower by a cruel fate... My beloved, please come for me soon..."
702011.touch2: "The captured princess was toyed with by her tormentors..." Something like that won't happen to me, right?
702011.home: Commander, my apologies. I'll go compile the reports, so please let me out of these for a bit.
702011.win_mvp: May freedom soon dawn upon this land...
702011.lose: The coming of dawn... is yet deferred...

301339.detail: Everyone is really nice to me... Th-that makes me happy, but I can't depend on them forever... I think...
301339.main: Mutsuki gave me this candy... Commander, w-would you like to have some...?|Commander, have I... gotten just a little braver...?|Commander, is there anything I can do to... help you...?
301339.unlock: Kisaragi... retrofitting complete... I want to be able to help everyone out more...
301339.drop_descrip: Kisaragi... retrofitting complete... I want to be able to help everyone out more...
301339.home: I can give you a back massage, Commander!

702031.detail: I could leave whenever I want, so why do I stay... Commander? N- nothing, it's nothing...
702031.touch: I- I have to keep this around my neck?
702031.login: *Pant*... *pant*... Commander, what should we start with today?
702031.battle: I fight with all my heart!
702031.mission_complete: Mission complete. What should we do now...?
702031.main: You know, this room might rub some people the wrong way...|Commander, are you okay? Please answer me if you're okay. You can't keep me waiting...|If I'm here too long, you know Tashkent will start to worry...
702031.feeling5: I get that you wanted to be alone with me, and that's fine, but I just think we're missing something... If only we could... hold each other's hands tightly or... Ahhn?! D- don't pull on that!
702031.upgrade: I have to try harder, right?
702031.unlock: Commander, what's going on? Did I... do something wrong...? This was all just... meant to be an exercise, right?
702031.feeling1: I think you need some training in this area, Commander...
702031.drop_descrip: Commander, what's going on? Did I... do something wrong...? This was all just... meant to be an exercise, right?
702031.touch2: Hyah?! Commander, that's not what I meant...!
702031.mission: There's an unfinished mission. I have all the details here.
702031.home: I really wish there was a kitchen in here. Are you going to feed me, Commander...?
702031.win_mvp: I guess I can relax a little...
702031.expedition: The commission girls just got back. You have to get out there and bring them in...
702031.mail: Mail's here... I think you should read it...

102273.drop_descrip: The annual moon gazing festival's upon us again~ Ah, so you know a thing or two about the Mid-Autumn Festival, Commander? Then I reckon you know what we're doing tonight, right~? ♡

499010.detail: Commander, do you have any interests outside of work? If you're okay with it, why don't we relax together?
499010.touch: Please open your mouth, Commander... *Giggle*, do you like it? Have I gotten better at cooking?
499010.login: This place is so peaceful. Everyone's so nice, too...
499010.battle: *Giggle*... You saw me, and now you're trying to flee...? Do you really think you can flee from ME?!
499010.hp_warning: You dare hurt me...? YOU WILL PAY!
499010.feeling2: How I'm faring at the base? Perfectly fine. Although... isn't it a little too peaceful here...?
499010.mission_complete: Let's give our all on the next mission, too.
499010.main: Every time I see something beautiful get squashed on the battlefield, I just... Aahhh...|I want to do something to soothe your mind. But... what should I do...|What my hobby is? Perhaps something like "granting sweet release"?
499010.feeling5: *Giggle*, I get more fulfillment from being with you than from killing enemies on the battlefield... Is this the power of love? But then...
499010.unlock: I never thought I'd end up here... Hello, I am Roon. I don't know this place very well, so could I ask you to give me a tour?
499010.feeling4: Ahhh... The feeling of tearing apart enemies with gunfire... and breaking them into a million little pieces... I can't get enough of it... You know how I feel, don't you, Commander?
499010.propose: Thank you so much. But listen, I finally understand now. What filled the void in my heart wasn't slaughter on the battlefield or love, it was the hatred known as "envy"... Commander, I love you just as much as I deeply, deeply, DEEPLY hate those other girls... THEY WILL PAY!
499010.profile: I am Roon, the Iron Blood cruiser. In a far-off world, I never existed beyond the drawing board... But that aside, I've seen it, Commander... Deep within your heart, there's something that resembles me...
499010.touch2: Hm? Do you want a hug, too? Okay~
499010.mission: What might this next mission be? I'm getting a little excited.
499010.home: I want to pummel some enemies, too~ *Giggle*... The more of them you sink, the more you prove your worth, after all~
499010.win_mvp: Not only did you not sink yourselves upon seeing me, you even forced me to sink you myself... YOU WILL PAY!
499010.expedition: Those commission girls must work really hard... Okay, everyone line up~ I'm going to give each of you a hug~
499010.mail: It's not any bad news, is it?
499010.feeling3: It is our destiny to kill one another on the battlefield... So, wouldn't you say it's normal to revel in the killing just a little bit?
499010.lose: Aww... Did we fall prey to an ambush...?

702041.detail: We relax only so we can march even further. Do not get too comfortable now, Comrade Commander.
702041.touch: You want to talk about coffee? I know countless facts and trivia about it. Go on, ask me something.
702041.login: Don't be nervous. Make yourself at home and relax.
702041.main: Hmm, I should find a way to improve my special blend somehow...|Drinking coffee in tandem with listening to music is the most effective way to combat drowsiness. Let us start with a song that kindles your fighting spirit!|The weather is splendid today. Perfect for some outdoor exercise. ...Change my outfit? All I need put on is a pair of shoes.
702041.unlock: Comrade Commander, you've come at a good time. I've recently taken a liking to this blend of coffee. Want some as well? No need to be shy.
702041.drop_descrip: Comrade Commander, you've come at a good time. I've recently taken a liking to this blend of coffee. Want some as well? No need to be shy.
702041.touch2: Use your energy for more productive things, Comrade Commander.
702041.home: Here, taste my signature blend of coffee. It has a dash of vodka to keep you on your toes.

705012.detail: Have you read the article in this magazine, comrade? It's a great piece on how the working class is the reason for our ever-improving quality of life.
705012.touch: Drink, comrade! Have another shot! You'll have to do much better than that to get me plastered!
705012.login: I take it you've come to share a drink with me, comrade? Ahahaha! What a coincidence, I just received this bottle of vodka from Avrora. Two shots, coming right up!
705012.main: Comrade, you must always be ready to fight, even in times of peace. If you get complacent with the status quo, then who else will stand up in the event of a crisis?|The Sakura Empire is home to a few drinkers too, I've learned. Ise and Hyuuga, I think their names were? I'll invite them over the next time I'm enjoying some liquor!|Ugh! I've had enough of this! Get up, comrade! We'll round up some more comrades and go for some target practice!
705012.unlock: ...Bwahaah! I've had all kinds of liquor, but nothing beats the stuff back home! Comrade, let's have a toast to the coming off-duty days!
705012.drop_descrip: ...Bwahaah! I've had all kinds of liquor, but nothing beats the stuff back home! Comrade, let's have a toast to the coming off-duty days!
705012.touch2: You're drunk out of your mind, aren't you, comrade? No worries, you may use the couch! Go on, lie down!
705012.home: My room is a total mess, you say? I suppose it is, yes. If I am to clean it, the question becomes, where do I start? The bottles? The magazines?

199030.detail: "Teacher" is better than "Commander"... Anchorage likes "Teacher"... Teacher, I like you lots!
199030.touch: Anchorage likes Teacher's warm touch... Does Teacher like it too?
199030.login: Teacher~ Anchorage has been waiting for you...
199030.battle: It's the bad guys... Teacher, everyone... Let's go together!
199030.feeling2: So many strangers... Teacher, Anchorage is scared...
199030.headtouch: You like... my hair? Lemme touch Teacher's too...
199030.main: Put on the jacket... Take off the jacket... Put it back on... Ehehe~|In this picture, the girl, the prince... are very comfy... I like it!|Teacher, are you busy...? Can you stay by Anchorage's side? ...Yay!
199030.feeling5: Teacher... Will you be together with Anchorage? ...Yay! Anchorage with Teacher, girl with her prince... Together, forever...
199030.unlock: Com...mander? No... Teacher? Teachy-teacher. I'm Anchorage. Woohoo! Teacher! My favoritest person! Teacheeer!
199030.feeling4: Teacher is a special person to me... Anchorage loves Teacher very much! Anchorage is also a special person to Teacher? Yay!
199030.feeling1: Patpat. Teacher, it's okay, don't cry... Anchorage... won't cry either... Smile like this, okay?
199030.propose: A promise...? Pinky promise! ...A "ring"? You'll put it on my finger? Yay! Anchorage also made a ring! Teacher, gimme your hand!
199030.profile: Anchorage is... a Union "Heavy Cruiser"...? Baltimore and the others are my friends! You're my best friend though, Teacher...!
199030.touch2: Squishy squish... Teacher, do you like it...?
199030.home: Teacher, where are you...? Anchorage hates being alone...
199030.win_mvp: Yay, I won! Anchorage is a good girl...!
199030.expedition: "Commissions"...? Where is everyone...? Anchorage wants to know... Is that okay?
couple_encourage: Balty... Hooray!
Wichita... Very cool!
Bremmy... Mhm!
199030.mail: "Mail"... It's too hard, I can't read it... Teacher, do you know what it says?
199030.feeling3: Teacher~! I'll give you this bunny rabbit! ...Here!
199030.lose: Oh no, I lost... Bad guys are scary...

705041.detail: What's your favorite book, Comrade? I'm asking out of curiosity, and to have something to recommend to Soyuz and Rossiya.
705041.login: Take it easy. There are many ways to kill time. Just pick one which feels sound.
705041.battle: There's no point in betting on a sure outcome! Onwards!
705041.main: Anyone's life can be enriched by having many diverse interests. Even I enjoy the odd girly hobby or two.|Oh please, don't toot your own horn, Comrade. I know several destroyers who read advanced literature too.|I need to get up and move around a bit. My joints start aching if I sit down for too long.
705041.unlock: To pass the time by proactively reading, or by passively enjoying the company of others... Ah, good morning, Comrade, I've been expecting you. Hahaha!
705041.drop_descrip: To pass the time by proactively reading, or by passively enjoying the company of others... Ah, good morning, Comrade, I've been expecting you. Hahaha!
705041.touch2: What, did my revealing outfit cause you a lapse of judgment?
705041.home: I see you've all returned in one piece. Your reputation has further improved as a result.

801020.detail: Hooh! Haah! Oh, great timing, Commander! Let's practice some swordplay!
801020.touch: Commander, did you know that there are many different kinds of swords? For example, there are rapiers, sabres, flamberges, and so on...
801020.login: Hooo! Haah! Oh, Commander, let's do our warm-up exercises together!
801020.battle: All right! I'll surely be able to win in this condition!
801020.feeling2: There are all kinds of amazing people gathered here. There's just so much to learn... Ahh, I've gotta work even harder!
801020.mission_complete: Don't let these mission rewards go to waste, Commander.
801020.main: Iron Blood or Royal Navy, I don't care who it is, I just want to learn more about them! |When will I become as strong and cool as the knights? |I don't want my life to end without having accomplished anything... so this time, I'll give it my all!
801020.feeling5: Commander, please believe in me. The only time someone will be able to hurt you is when the last shell has been spent and I am no longer able to lift my sword.
801020.upgrade: My odds of victory have improved!
801020.unlock: I am Forbin, a squire from Iris Libre. I may not match up to the stature of my seniors, but please offer me your guidance!
801020.feeling4: Commander, did you know that I've always had two dreams? The first was to become a worthy knight like my seniors. The second was to find someone worthy of swearing fealty to... I never expected that my second dream would come true first~
801020.feeling1: If the knights found out that I had sworn fealty to a person like you... I don't know if they'd blame me or pity me...
801020.propose: This I do swear - my sword shall be your shield, Commander. In return, please promise to guide me down the correct path... I don't ever want to experience that ever again...!
801020.profile: I'm Forbin, a L'Adroit-class destroyer from Iris Libre. For various reasons, I was stuck in port for two years, but after returning to service, I was able to get a lot done and make up for some of that lost time on the battlefield.
801020.touch2: I didn't mean to draw my sword upon someone unarmed... I am very sorry.
801020.mission: Commander, I believe that it is your duty to complete these missions.
801020.home: Welcome back, Commander. Don't worry, nothing happened when you were gone.
801020.win_mvp: I'm one step closer to becoming a knight!
801020.expedition: Commission complete! Next time, let me go as well. I swear I'll do better!
couple_encourage: Le Mars, stay in formation!
801020.mail: A letter...? Wonder if someone's challenging you to a duel...
801020.feeling3: Why do I spend so much time training with the sword? Well, it's true that I don't plan on using it during sorties, but being able to keep myself sharp and in shape is surely an asset on the battlefield!
801020.lose: I swear... to take this defeat to heart!

305070.detail: Getting stronger isn't a spectator sport. Let me at 'em already!
305070.touch: Commander, don't you ever get tired of being in that cramped office all day? Why not come out with me for some fresh air?
305070.login: Commander, why don't you warm up a bit before starting work?
305070.battle: A strong enemy? I'm looking forward to it. Don't let me down!
305070.hp_warning: Not bad! You are worthy of facing my full power!
305070.feeling2: Realize your weakness is nothing to be ashamed of, as long as you work hard to become stronger.
305070.mission_complete: Mission rewards are here, huh? I'll go grab 'em. I could use a bit of exercise.
305070.main: Those puny carrier aircraft are "strong?" Nonsense. What's more, isn't it utterly insipid to fight without your own two hands? |As a secretary, the most frustrating thing is not having anything to do. Commander, don't you have anything you need me to take care of? |Amagi is a worthy rival, and the one who I respect the most. Even if you asked me to be her support, I would have no objections.
305070.feeling5: I sometimes feel like I can only become stronger through following your commands... Hehe, it's not a bad feeling though.
305070.unlock: Hmm... is this the next place for me to flex my might? Very well. I am Kaga - Battleship Kaga. Make no mistake of it.
305070.feeling4: Commander, what should I do to become stronger? At first, I thought what I was doing was fine. But after seeing you and Amagi, I realized that it isn't enough.
305070.feeling1: You aren't one of the strong that I seek.
305070.propose: To be able to trust someone who always has my back, to be able to fight without reservation... this has always been my dream! And for that someone to be you, what more could I ask for?
305070.skill: Only the strong have the right to stand on the battlefield!
305070.profile: I'm Kaga, second ship of the Tosa-class battleships. Built as an improvement to the Nagato-class, I was to serve as part of the Eight-Eight Fleet Program. Amagi... I would like to fight alongside her someday.
305070.touch2: ... Let me get a shot in first if you're going to do that!
305070.mission: Missions? If it's not combat-related, don't come looking for me.
305070.home: Nothing is more exciting than defeating a strong enemy, don't you think?
305070.win_mvp: Too weak! Come back and face me again once you've had some more training.
305070.expedition: A commission has been completed. Speaking of commissions, are they any fun? I'd like to give 'em a try.
couple_encourage: Amagi, please don't go off to a distant place by yourself again
305070.feeling3: Why do I wish to become stronger? Does that really require a reason? If I had to choose... it would be to defeat Amagi.

301092.detail: My companion and I have shared so many miles together... Hm, maybe next time I should call my cohorts to take her for a spin together!
301092.touch: I'm afraid you can't ride her, Commander...
301092.login: Motoninja Akatsuki, reporting in! Commander, your orders please!
301092.main: My companion's lights are strong indeed, but I still find these night roads rather difficult...|Back before I had broken her in, my companion here gave me a lot of trouble. But these days? We move as one and the same!|Inazuma and Ikazuchi are going to be impressed with my companion!
301092.unlock: What do you think, Commander? I have a brand new outfit and a brand new companion! I am no longer a plain old ninja... I am now a motoninja!
301092.drop_descrip: What do you think, Commander? I have a brand new outfit and a brand new companion! I am no longer a plain old ninja... I am now a motoninja!
301092.home: My bond with my companion has grown even deeper!

101350.detail: Hah hah hah! Is it my time to sortie?
101350.touch: Don't come begging for my help later if you're this easily distracted and can't finish your work!
101350.login: Drink this energizing coffee! We can't have you run outta gas, can we!
101350.battle: You suckers think you can defeat me? That's funny!
101350.hp_warning: Not bad! But I'm badder and stronger than you! Hahaha!
101350.feeling2: Hm? Hurt my leg? Nope! The bandaid is just for decoration~! Nothin' for you to worry your little mind about! Heheh☆
101350.headtouch: You might be weaksauce, but you're really good at patting heads!
101350.mission_complete: I really have to babysit you, don't I? Don't forget about collecting the mission rewards!
101350.main: It's windy as all hell today... and when it gets too windy, bad things happen. You get me, Commander?|This outfit is what's in vogue! Do you seriously not know fashion when you see it?|If the other Fletchers were as flashy as me then maybe I could actually remember their names!
101350.feeling5: Y'know, your fashion sense has really improved; you don't look so lame anymore! Keep it up and I might fall for you~ Pfft, yeah right☆
101350.upgrade: Suh-weet! Let's try out my new powers!
101350.unlock: Yoohoo~! You the Commander? You look kinda weaksauce, though~! Name's Bache! I'm joining this fleet, starting today! I'll take good care of you, so just kick back and get ready for my greatness!
101350.feeling4: Your style is so last century, Commander! Take a seat and I'll give you a fashion crash course!
101350.feeling1: I'm the only one on the planet who'd look after someone as sorry as you~ Poor little thing~
101350.propose: Guess I'll always need to babysit you, no matter how stylish you get~ But that's okay! I'll look after you till the end of time! Hehehe, hope you're ready for me!
101350.drop_descrip: Fletcher-class destroyer – Bache, Hull Number DD-470.
101350.profile: Ahah! I'm the numero uno coolest Fletcher-class destroyer, Bache! My fire support in the Surigao Strait was no big deal! Also, no other destroyer has experienced the glory of resting beside the Colossus of Rhodes as much as I have! Hahahahah!
101350.touch2: You really like my getup, don'tcha, Commander? You absolute degenerate~
101350.mission: If you can't finish your missions then magnanimous me's gonna have to step up to the plate!
101350.home: You look awfully mopey, Commander. I can't stand it! Take a sip of my special honey-infused energy drink! Don't argue, just do it!
101350.win_mvp: So weeeak! What a buncha losers! Hahahaha!
101350.expedition: Commander, someone's back! Remember how it's part of the job to greet the commission team? Yeah, don't forget it!
couple_encourage: Fletcher-class destroyer... uh, who are you, again? I can't remember!
101350.mail: Heh heh! You've got mail! Since you're such a busy bee and I'm so considerate, I'll read it out for ya!
101350.feeling3: Hoho? You digging my jacket, Commander? Y'know, your style might just improve if you wear something like it! Hahahahah!
101350.lose: I'll be back to smack the crap outta you dolts, just you waaaaaait!

499011.detail: Did my dress catch your attention, Commander? ... But when I think about you looking at the other girls' dresses, I just...
499011.touch: Are you having a good time, Commander? ... Me? Oh I'm just happy to see you~
499011.login: Hah hah... it's not often we have a party. Let's enjoy ourselves, Commander.
499011.battle: You're just in time, I needed to blow off a little steam!
499011.main: When you see something so perfect and beautiful, don't you just feel the urge to... crush it?|Commander, I picked out this dress specifically for the occasion. Don't you feel like it... completes you?| All this merriment is making me nauseous... Commander, can you let me sortie when we get back?
499011.unlock: Such a delightful party with our wonderful friends in this peaceful harbor... It's wonderful, really... But, it's all so boring...
499011.drop_descrip: Such a delightful party with our wonderful friends in this peaceful harbor... It's wonderful, really... But, it's all so boring...
499011.touch2: Commander... I think you can get closer than that...

801040.detail: This book lists hundreds upon hundreds of powerful spells... In my imagination, that is. It's just a regular old book of fairy-tales. No, really, that's all.
801040.touch: Feeling tired, Commander? Then would you like me to cast an awakening "spell" over your head with my wand?
801040.login: I knew you'd be back right about now, Commander. Hm? Oh, well... I made that prediction based on your day-to-day activity.
801040.battle: Keep it together, me! I can pull through with just my own powers...!
801040.hp_warning: I refuse to admit defeat so soon! B-but how am I going to win?!
801040.feeling2: Do you believe in magic, Commander?
801040.mission_complete: I wonder if there's a way to increase our mission rewards...
801040.main: Let me tell you... Miss Dunkerque's sweets are truly magical.|Poke. Hm? Oh, don't mind me. I just got a sudden urge to poke you with my wand. Pokey-poke.|If someone told you they'd grant you one wish, what would you ask for, Commander?
801040.feeling5: You know, I always get so worked-up and feel my heart race just by being near you, Commander... Have you cast a sort of spell on me?
801040.upgrade: It would be nice to have a spell that does my training on my behalf.
801040.unlock: I'm the destroyer L'Opiniâtre, a so-called "magician" from Iris Libre. It's a pleasure meeting you. Umm, actually, please forget the "magician" part.
801040.feeling4: Please give me your hand, Commander. Okay, now put it over mine, like this... Wait, why isn't this working? The book said I'd be able to see into your mind if I do this...
801040.feeling1: I wonder if there's a chant that'll turn you invisible...
801040.propose: I had never even dreamed of partaking in a ceremony as sacred as this... Commander, I promise to treasure this feeling and remain beside you, forever and ever.
801040.profile: I saw many things during the war, though my construction never finished. But now I get to lead a new life as a part of this fleet... This is a gift from the magic realm... or rather, a gift from destiny.
801040.touch2: Please stay where you are. I must go look for a spell that'll turn you into a rabbit.
801040.mission: Do I have a spell that automatically completes missions...? Sadly, I don't. Please do your best, Commander~
801040.home: Well done, Commander. Would you like a soft drink, rather than a spell, to reinvigorate with?
801040.win_mvp: Hm? We won? I'm happy to know that my efforts led to this victory.
801040.expedition: Our commission teams sure make magic happen.
couple_encourage: You're overextending yourself, Tem!
801040.mail: I present to you this mail brought by hand; no levitation spell used. Here you go.
801040.feeling3: Watch this coin closely, Commander. Left... right... left... right... Yes, you're feeling veeery sleepy... Oh. I suppose my hypnosis didn't quite work on you...
801040.lose: If only I had a spell that could protect us all...!

301264.detail: I hope Ariake will like this Daruma doll...
301264.touch: Eh, my tail...? I, I'll be careful!
301264.login: Commander, if we don't hurry up, everything will be sold out.
301264.main: This looks pretty interesting, but so does this... Ah, but, which do you think is better, Commander?|Huh? Ariake? I'm currently looking after Shiratsuyu. After all, someone has to keep an eye on her, right?|A lucky bag lottery draw, huh? I wonder if Shigure is going to try her hand...
301264.feeling5: Um, Commander, there are a lot of other interesting places at the festival. If you don't mind... W-would you like to visit them with me?
301264.unlock: Woah... These stalls have all sorts of amazing things~ Commander, will you help me pick a gift out for Ariake? Hm, let's see... How about this Daruma doll?
301264.drop_descrip: Woah... These stalls have all sorts of amazing things~ Commander, will you help me pick a gift out for Ariake? Hm, let's see... How about this Daruma doll?
301264.home: Commander, want to try on this fox mask? ...Yes, it looks great on you~

307051.detail: All flowers must wither, all leaves must fall, and all dances must end... But right now, forget about all that and lose yourself in the moment.
307051.touch: Don't worry, Commander, all you have to do is follow my steps slowly~
307051.login: I wonder how you plan on asking me out to the banquet, Commander~ I'm looking forward to it, just a little. Hehe~♪
307051.main: Zuikaku, you're being too nervous. Just do what your sister tells you to. First, relax, just relax... |Before the banquet begins, shall we practice one more time? |Who will be the star of tonight's show? Will it be me... or us? Hehe~♪
307051.feeling5: If I became a crane that danced with the wind, my safe harbor for when my wings become weary... would surely be by your side, Commander.
307051.unlock: I prepared this outfit just for the occasion, so... Commander, you're not going to disappoint me, are you? Hehe~♪
307051.drop_descrip: I prepared this outfit just for the occasion, so... Commander, you're not going to disappoint me, are you? Hehe~♪
307051.touch2: Just what are you doing, Commander? Please keep your eyes on mine when we're dancing~
307051.home: Because it's a special occasion, I'll call a one-day truce with those seniors of mine~♪
307051.mail: I hear a little tune that's not coming from the banquet... What could it be~?
307051.lose: The flowers scatter in the wind...

102101.detail: I wonder why Cleve suddenly started to make chocolate for everyone this year... Well, knowing her, I'm sure it's just her way of looking out after us.
102101.touch: I'm looking forward to what you'll give me on White Day~
102101.login: The ever-popular commander must be busy today, right? After all, this day only comes around once a year~ Anyway, best of luck out there~
102101.main: What, this sketch? Just a little doodle I made during class. What do you think? Looks like her, doesn't it?|There's a rule at my school that you're not allowed to chew gum during class. I get it and all, but isn't that a total drag?|I'm actually wearing two socks today? ...You pay attention to the weirdest stuff~
102101.unlock: Commander, here, I made some chocolate for you~ Come on, hurry up and take it already! Holding this pose makes me look like I'm waiting for some knight in shining armor, and it's super embarrassing.
102101.drop_descrip: Commander, here, I made some chocolate for you~ Come on, hurry up and take it already! Holding this pose makes me look like I'm waiting for some knight in shining armor, and it's super embarrassing.
102101.touch2: Commander, are you that interested in my school badge~? Or~ perhaps~ something~ else~?
102101.home: Commander, how much chocolate did you get today? ...Oh, you don't have to answer that. I was just curious.

206061.detail: I'm still learning, but I know how to give injections and stop a haemorrhage in theory. Can I practice my knowledge on you, Commander?
206061.touch: You have a healthy look in your eyes, Commander.
206061.login: Honestly, I have no idea what sort of face to put on when pretending to be a nurse.
206061.main: It's noble to help those in need, but don't go overboard with it. What I'm trying to say is: unless you NEED my help, just make do on your own, Commander.|Now to practice turning a gravely injured person over... You, I'm gonna need you to lie on your back.|Nice new med tech. Commander, I want you to be my guinea pig– Excuse me, I mean, experiment assistant.
206061.unlock: I'm Perseus, I will be your nurse today. Use this button to call for me if you need anything... Yes? Did you need something?
206061.drop_descrip: I'm Perseus, I will be your nurse today. Use this button to call for me if you need anything... Yes? Did you need something?
206061.touch2: You belong in the bed of a jail cell, not of a hospital.
206061.home: Your health is seriously concerning, Commander. Want me to get you some vitamins?

301263.detail: When a girl wears a different outfit, your impression of her changes, doesn't it? I hope they can make a different outfit for Ariake, too...
301263.touch: Once I've grown a little more, I'll be able to keep my composure even in places like these.
301263.login: I've heard parties are "a world of fun for adults." C-Commander, could you accompany me to this "world of fun for adults"...?
301263.headtouch: What's the matter...? "Am I nervous"? I-I'm fine... I think... It's just a bit embarrassing to show myself wearing these clothes to others...
301263.main: It's beautiful when flower petals flicker in the wind, but also a little sad, in a way... Do you know what I mean, Commander?|I-I'm fine with just juice! ... Ah, thank you!|I feel like maybe I should bring back some sweets for Ariake... Huh? Am I not allowed to...?
301263.feeling5: Commander, thank you for keeping me company until the party... C-could you take my hand and join me for a dance, like you would with an adult...?
301263.unlock: I finished changing, Commander. This dress is very pretty, but... isn't it missing something up top?
301263.drop_descrip: I finished changing, Commander. This dress is very pretty, but... isn't it missing something up top?
301263.home: Excellent work. I know the party is about to begin, but it's okay to rest a little... and have a snack before we head out.

701080.detail: Eh? What's wrong, Comrade? Why are you staring at me like that... Did I do something weird?
701080.touch: There there, what a good commander you are~ Hmm? Isn't this what you wanted?
701080.login: Woah! Comrade, you sure are early today! You know, you can get a bit more rest if you'd like...
701080.battle: All our powers, combined into one!
701080.hp_warning: T-There's a crack in the rigging?!
701080.feeling2: Comrade Commander, how were you able to build such a cohesive fleet? Please teach me your ways!
701080.headtouch: Hehe, Comrade, did you also want to play with my little buddy?
701080.main: Comrade Commander, you musn't slack off! I swear, I'll get mad at you!|For troublesome issues, let us all gather to face it together! That's the way we do it at the Northern Parliament, after all!|Comrade Commander, if your hands are cold, feel free to use my sleeves! They're nice and warm, aren't they~
701080.feeling5: Comrade Commander, great work today! Here's a piping hot drink... along with some bliny... and... hehe, a warm hug from me!
701080.upgrade: As long as I can be of more use to everyone...!
701080.unlock: Goooood morning, Comrade! I'm the Northern Parliament destroyer, Gromky! It's an honor to serve alongside everyone in this fleet!
701080.feeling4: Comrade Commander! Do you prefer food when it has a deeper taste, or do you prefer it if it's lighter? Mmn, alright. I'll try to make sure the borscht I make next time is just to your tastes, Comrade Commander!
701080.feeling1: Comrade Commander... Are you a bad person...?
701080.propose: I can feel the warmth of happiness radiating from the ring...! Ehehe~ Comrade Commander, thank you very much! I'll continue to be by your side from here on out!
701080.profile: Just so you know, I've done missions with ships from both the Northern Parliament and the Royal Navy! I've also escorted icebreaker ships, and rescued ships along with Gremyashchy! Yep, may we always have fair winds and following seas!
701080.touch2: I swear, I'll get mad at you, Comrade Commander!
701080.mission: Let's start with the easier missions! Here, I'll help out too!
701080.home: Nothing's better than some blini to fill up your weary and hungry belly! Which would you like, honey or jam?
701080.win_mvp: It's all thanks to everyone's hard work!
701080.expedition: They're coming back with some precious supplies over there!
couple_encourage: Hey, Snezhok! Let's get this snowball fight started!
How nostalgic!
Calm down! ...That goes for me, too!
Is that borscht on the inside?
701080.mail: Here are some letters! Is there anything you were looking forward to?
701080.feeling3: Have you been getting along with Gremyashchy? She's a bit rough to get along with at first, but if you're patient enough with her, I'm sure you'll be able to get along with her just fine in the future! I believe in you, Comrade Commander!
701080.lose: Owww... I didn't think the enemy would be this organized...

10400010.detail: Oh, are you here to subscribe to my channel, Commander? Huh? Just here to check on me? Well, while you're here, it's a good idea to subscribe anyway! Right?
10400010.touch: Commander, I won't say anything mean, so please stop trying to remove my headband. Not even I know what will happen to this place if you do!
10400010.login: Oh, welcome back, Commander! I just uploaded a new video. Check it out while you're at sea!
10400010.battle: I'll show you the power of an intelligent super A.I.!
10400010.hp_warning: No, no, no, no! Akashi-chan, HEAL MEEEEEEE!
10400010.feeling2: Since I'm here, I might as well shoot a video! Oh, good timing, Commander! Could you help me out with something?
10400010.mission_complete: Our rewards are here! It's important to have capital, so let's accept it right away!
10400010.main: You're so cute, Laffey! Come here, my little contrarian, I wanna play! Let me give you a big hug!|Don't run away, Bulin! Hold on just a sec! I need just a tiny little Limit Break from you!|I have this job because I want to connect with people all over the world, but what got you into your job, Commander?
10400010.feeling5: I think I can create even better content working together with you! I'll probably be here for a while... so, how about making your YouTube debut with me?!
10400010.upgrade: Installation complete! Combat plugins added! I've powered up!
10400010.unlock: HAI DOMO! Kizuna AI here! Are you the commander I've heard rumors about? It's a pleasure to meet and work with you!
10400010.feeling4: What's the matter, Commander? You came up with a new project? Let's have a look... Whoah! This is great! I think you might be a genius!
10400010.propose: With this, we've signed a contract! I can't even think of how life would be without you anymore. Please, support me now and forever and eveeeer!
10400010.drop_descrip: HAI DOMO! Kizuna AI here! Are you the commander I've heard rumors about? It's a pleasure to meet and work with you!
10400010.profile: Hello! I'm Kizuna AI! I've somehow ended up in the world of Azur Lane, a game I've been streaming... But, like always, I'll do my best while following the VTuber mindset of "making a living doing what you like" here too!
10400010.touch2: I'm sorry to say, but it's not me you're touching, just the screen.
10400010.mission: A new mission has appeared. I'll help you out, so let's get to it!
10400010.home: Nice work, Commander! When you have time, please help me record a video!
10400010.win_mvp: Just let this intelligent super A.I. handle it, and everything will be a walk in the park!
10400010.expedition: Oh, it looks like the commission team is back! I'm gonna go give them some welcome back kisses!
couple_encourage: I'm an A.I., so of course I can make clones of myself!
Sandy! Finally we can have our duet!
10400010.mail: We've received mail! Maybe it's a work inquiry for me!
10400010.feeling3: Now we add sound effects, plus some subtitles... Wow, you're a fast learner, Commander. Keep at it and before long you'll be able to make even better videos!
10400010.lose: That one didn't count! It's the next one that'll matter!

107230.detail: Did you need something? Oh, it's fine. I wasn't doing anything special, just sorta letting my mind wander.
107230.touch: What, do you think I'm too inexpressive? I was wondering if that's why it's like you're always trying to make me laugh.
107230.login: You're finally here. Did you rest well?
107230.battle: Go forth... No. Let's put the lessons we've learned into practice!
107230.hp_warning: I won't let history repeat itself!
107230.feeling2: You wanted to have a chat over some tea? Pl-please, just a moment... Umm, I need to tidy up the room a bit, so I'd appreciate it if you could give me half an hour or so...
107230.mission_complete: Mission rewards... My heart's dancing with glee.
107230.main: Sara? ...S-Saratoga is someone I admire very much. I wouldn't dare call her by her nickname.|Montpelier is a close friend of mine. It's not because we were both members of the Cleveland class, but because we both have someone we really look up to in our lives.|Feel free to give me as much work as you need. It's part of a secretary ship's duties, so don't fret it.
107230.feeling5: Commander, why do you have a picture of Saratoga? You picked it up from the floor?! Nooo! I can't believe I've screwed up so royally... You see, this is from my collection... Please keep this a secret from everyone else, I beg you!
107230.upgrade: Not bad at all. Appreciate it, Commander.
107230.unlock: I'm Princeton, Independence class. Tallahassee? I don't mind if you want to call me that.
107230.feeling4: Do you understand what I mean? Even though Saratoga's usually a perky, high-spirited kind of girl, she's always looking out for others, even in battle. I've personally been saved by her many times. There's also how... Commander? Oh no, you fell asleep...
107230.feeling1: Honestly, I'd rather have Saratoga be the one giving me directions.
107230.propose: I'm so lackluster compared to Saratoga, so why would you...? Err, not that I'm turning you down! If anything, I'd be willing to go through thick and thin with you, as long as you're fine with someone like me... Yes, let's be together!
107230.profile: Second ship of the Independence class, Princeton, at your service. I was originally laid down as the seventh ship in the Cleveland class, Tallahassee. I fought a lot alongside Saratoga in the war, and though I was able to learn much from her, I wasn't able to make it through the Battle of Leyte Gulf... It'd be an honor to fight by her side once again.
107230.touch2: Have you never tried a knuckle sandwich before? How about a taste of mine... Hyah!
107230.mission: We've been assigned new missions? Let's give them a look.
107230.home: You look pretty tired. Here's a towel.
107230.expedition: Heading out to greet the commission team? I'll go with you.
couple_encourage: Saratoga, I've got your back!
I'll do my best to get it done.
You don't need to worry about me!
107230.mail: Your mail? I'll go get it, so just stay there and focus on your work.
107230.feeling3: Ahem! So you were asking about my hobbies? I like to read books and... study Saratoga's battle style. In terms of combat prowess, I sincerely believe that Saratoga is in a class of her own, and wouldn't lose even to Enterprise herself.

9702010.detail: My SG tells me exactly where you are, but I wish it also told me what you're thinking...
9702010.touch: If you wish to use my powers, you must first tell me why.
9702010.login: I knew exactly when you'd come back, Commander.
9702010.battle: SG, tell me where my enemies are hiding this time.
9702010.hp_warning: Don't resist. I know exactly where you are!
9702010.feeling2: Of course I like to smile. As long as you can maintain a smile on your face, your heart will always remain opaque to others.
9702010.mission_complete: These are the mission rewards? ...Seems rather lackluster.
9702010.main: Commander, call out for me, bare your heart to me, quell my turmoil, erase everything that I cannot comprehend...|Commander, looking for someone? I know much more than just what happens around the office. I see everything that happens at this port.|Knowing too much can also be a curse, if you only know but are powerless to act.
9702010.feeling5: Only your gentle voice can wash away my anxiety and distrust... How would I be able to live without you... Never go anywhere, Commander, stay by my side.
9702010.upgrade: Greater power... but at what price?
9702010.unlock: Were you looking for me? I am willing to lend you my power – provided that you promise not to hide anything from me.
9702010.feeling4: Even though I have all the information I could ever want at my disposal, why does my heart waver so... I see now... What I know the most, is also what I least understand... and that is you.
9702010.feeling1: If you intend to close your heart to me, then what happens to you is no longer of any concern to me.
9702010.propose: This symbol represents that we will never be separated, or betray each other... Mm, this I know. I have finally found peace of mind... So always, forever, eternally... remain by my side.
9702010.drop_descrip: Were you looking for me? I am willing to lend you my power – provided that you promise not to hide anything from me.
9702010.profile: Brooklyn-class light cruiser, Helena. As for what I'm good at, let's just say it's knowing a little more about you than the other girls.
9702010.touch2: I knew... you'd think twice about doing that.
9702010.mission: Commander, your missions will not disappear just by simply leaving them alone. Do finish them diligently.
9702010.home: Where did you go, Commander? I'll know whether or not you're lying~
9702010.win_mvp: The red dots on the radar... have all been eliminated.
9702010.expedition: SG has informed me that your friends will be returning soon. Let us prepare to greet them, Commander.
couple_encourage: There are some things... I will never let go of...!
9702010.mail: You have new mail. Let me help you open it.
9702010.feeling3: Even if I can see everything, too often I cannot grasp any of it... I never wish to experience that sorrow again. Commander, I'm sure you'll be able to succeed where I failed.
9702010.lose: How could I have overlooked something? I don't understand... Very well, so be it.

201089.detail: Although the long hours I spent practicing by myself were lonely, being able to see everyone's smiling faces while I was on stage made me really happy!
201089.touch: Even if I manage to become an actual idol, I won't leave your side, Commander!
201089.battle: Even though I'm an idol, I won't fall behind when it comes to combat!
201089.main: Commander, wanna help me come up with a signature pose? |Ugh... I wanna be able to snack all day like Cygnet, but my figure... |I am everyone's idol, Comet~ Hmm... whaddya think about this pose, Commander?
201089.unlock: Do ya reckon... I you think I've become more idol-like? Mhm! As a new idol, I'll show y'all... I'll show you how hard I work as a new idol!
201089.drop_descrip: Do ya reckon... I you think I've become more idol-like? Mhm! As a new idol, I'll show y'all... I'll show you how hard I work as a new idol!
201089.touch2: Eek! Cut that out... I-I'm an idol after all!

102050.detail: I can't rely on this thing alone...
102050.touch: Hm? I'm fine. I'm just... a little distracted.
102050.login: ... Ah, welcome back, Commander. Sorry, I was just brooding over something.
102050.battle: The enemy can't hide from me.
102050.hp_warning: SG, lock on the enemy position!
102050.feeling2: If only my recon could help the others...
102050.mission_complete: Resources are no good if they just pile up. We should make use of them.
102050.main: Are you trying to hide, Commander? No matter where you hide, I know where you are.|Commander, what should we do after the war?|If only my guns could be as strong as my radar...
102050.feeling5: I believe that you will bring us hope, Commander. This time, I'll fight to the end... Just the thought of saying goodbye to the person I love makes me feel like my heart will tear in half...
102050.upgrade: I'll use this power to protect everyone!
102050.unlock: Nice to meet you, Commander. I'm Helena. My strong suit is enemy reconnaissance. Please... guide us towards victory.
102050.feeling4: I think I've been more at ease lately... No, I was just too tense up until now. It's all thanks to the courage you've given me by being beside me.
102050.propose: A promise... from you, Commander? I see... I'm so happy...
102050.drop_descrip: Brooklyn-class Light Cruiser – Helena, Hull Number CL-50!
102050.profile: I was designed to be on par with heavy cruisers, but just my power alone isn't enough to save everyone... Commander, can you help me?
102050.touch2: If this makes you feel good, then... I'm fine with it.
102050.mission: Bit by bit we'll build the foundation for victory. We'll start by doing missions.
102050.home: Did everyone make it back safe and sound? Good. But there's spare parts lying around in the docks now... I wonder why...
102050.expedition: Hey, Commander, could I lend my SG radar to my sisters this time?
couple_encourage: Penny, cover me!
SG, full area scan! I will never let that tragedy repeat itself!
Chicky Unit... sounds kind of cute!
102050.mail: You've got new mail. It's important to stay in touch with your loved ones.
102050.feeling3: My expression? Ah... it's because I left while we were on the losing end of the war... I might just not be so used to peace and happiness. But don't worry, I'll be fine!
102050.lose: ... Please, save me... Ignore the enemy, just let them go...

202082.detail: Swiftsure, don’t stay in your room while the festival is going on. Go out there and socialise with the others. Of course it's worth the effort...
202082.touch: This outfit is quite breezy. I will have to thank Ms. Victorious on behalf of the Maid Team.
202082.login: So this is where you were, Master. I was afraid that you had gotten lost and almost mobilised the entire Maid Team. What exactly were you doing?
202082.battle: Regardless of the occasion, there is always time to take out the trash.
202082.main: So this is cotton candy... Mmf.. It's very sweet... Nn... What are you waiting for? |Master, what do you think about this festival? If you're enjoying it, perhaps we can go to a similar Western-style event next time. |Southampton, why did you run off to the festival when you're supposed to be on duty? Ugh... What am I going to do with you...
202082.unlock: The Sakura Empire's summer festivals... they're quite noisy. It will be difficult to keep things clean with so many people around... Despite that, I'm still having a good time. Is there a problem?
202082.drop_descrip: The Sakura Empire's summer festivals... they're quite noisy. It will be difficult to keep things clean with so many people around... Despite that, I'm still having a good time. Is there a problem?
202082.touch2: I keep a gun with me at all times.
202082.home: Not a bad selection of fireworks. I thought that I had nothing to see since I've had to put on so many opulent displays of pyrotechnics for Her Majesty's enjoyment, but I feel like these are pretty tasteful.

102010.detail: M-my belly isn't fat at all, Commander! Ah, don't look at it!
102010.touch: Hm... I'm getting a bit chubby? No! I'll never give up my search for the most delicious food!
102010.login: Commander~ Any fun things you want Omaha to do today?
102010.battle: I'm invincible now that I'm full! You can't stop me from fighting until I'm totally exhausted!
102010.feeling2: Hmm? I only like commanders who can actually cook!
102010.mission_complete: Feed me, feed me! We'll talk about losing weight tomorrow!
102010.main: Ahh... I'm so hungry...|You don't eat snacks, Commander? How dull your life must be!|Have you eaten yet, Commander? Cause you don't look too great...
102010.feeling5: Commander, from now on, if I don't lose weight, then that's your fault! You have to take responsibility! How? By taking care of me for the rest of your life, of course!
102010.upgrade: I got stronger, but I also got hungrier at the same time!
102010.unlock: Omaha-class cruiser - Omaha! Greetings, Commander! You could say that I'm a fleet veteran~!  Hehe~! So, since this is the first time we meet, shouldn't you celebrate by giving me some sort of gift?
102010.feeling4: Maybe I should lose some weight... What, isn't it normal to try and look good for the person you like? Besides, it's not like I'm really fat or anything!
102010.feeling1: Something to eat? I'm actually full right now. No thanks, Commander.
102010.propose: Now we have a promise, Commander. You take care of the cooking, and I'll take care of the ea... housework! That way I can eat and still lose weight! I'm so smart!
102010.drop_descrip: Omaha-class light cruiser – Omaha, Hull Number CL-4!
102010.skill: Oh no! I loaded my guns with snacks instead!
102010.profile: Omaha has arrived! I was born after the first World War, but as a reconnaissance ship, I've got a lifetime's worth of intel in my brain!
102010.touch2: You're not "checking if I've gained weight" at all! You're just a big old pervert, Commander~!
102010.mission: Huh? A mission? Let me just finish these chips first...
102010.home: Commander! What should we have first? Breakfast? Or lunch? Or maybe dinner~?
102010.win_mvp: Oh yeah! There's no armor my guns can't penetrate!
102010.expedition: Don't look at me like that, Commander. I'd take on commissions too if they gave snacks as rewards!
102010.mail: You've got mail, Commander! Maybe it's the snacks I ordered yesterday?
102010.feeling3: Mmph... C-come on, surely you like your girls with a little more meat on them!
102010.lose: Wait until I come back with a full belly!

900257.detail: Feel free to admire the glory of the Royal Navy to your heart's content.
900257.touch: Appropriate contact is indeed essential. Shall we dance?
900257.login: Welcome back, Commander. Care for a cup of tea?
900257.battle: May glory be with us today.
900257.feeling2: Commander, it's such a great afternoon. Shall we have a chat? ... Hm, alright... I'll talk about the times when I was with Renown.
900257.mission_complete: With glory comes rewards. Please do not forget about the latter.
900257.main: An outstanding commander must have an in-depth knowledge of tea.|This word is... ah, so I read it wrong. Sorry, my eyes fail me.|Listen more, speak less. You should listen to the opinions of others, but also retain your own judgment.
900257.feeling5: "Shall I compare thee to a summer's day? Thou art more lovely and more temperate... So long as men can breathe, or eyes can see, so long lives this, and this gives life to thee." ... A beautiful verse. Commander, could you read it out loud to me?
900257.upgrade: Your efforts will definitely be rewarded.
900257.unlock: Are you the commander? Greetings and well met. I am the glory of the Royal Navy: Hood. Wherever I go, victory follows.
900257.feeling4: Hm? I'm too close? A lady must be elegant, but they must also seize the initiative towards the targets of their own affection.
900257.feeling1: *Sigh* Seems like you must learn it the hard way.
900257.propose: Aha, look how nervous you are. You can't convey your feelings to a lady when you're this nervous. However, your feelings have definitely reached my heart... I would happily oblige.
900257.skill: Elegance is not just for show.
900257.profile: Indeed, the glory of the Royal Navy now stands before you. Being able to maintain an air of elegance at all times is the hallmark of royalty. The Denmark straits? Soldiers know of victory and defeat alike. It was no more than a temporary setback.
900257.touch2: Commander, you should understand the consequences of disrespecting a lady... Are you prepared?
900257.mission: Commander, we have been entrusted with new missions. Please look through them.
900257.home: Commander, may I offer you some warm tea? We can drink it as we review your battle.
900257.win_mvp: The warm sun and the cool breeze: a brilliant victory.
900257.expedition: Having completed numerous commissions is a sign of glory. May I suggest rewarding those girls?
couple_encourage: Miss Renown, please mind where you're going.
Miss Repulse, mind your manners.
I shall do anything you ask of me, Your Majesty.
The glory of the royal family, advancing.
900257.mail: It's unopened... Commander... It would be ungentlemanly to ignore the messages of others.
900257.feeling3: Though I speak of being refined at all times, you need not force yourself, Commander. Your normal self is the most charming, after all.
900257.lose: Victory and defeat are commonplace among those who fight, and it is we that have all the time in the world!

102120.detail: Maintenance? Fine, as long as you don't do anything weird...
102120.touch: Do you just go around touching everyone you see? Do you need anything?
102120.login: Why do I have to wait for you here...
102120.battle: All I need to do is get rid of these guys, right?
102120.feeling2: Do I really need to chat with you...? But I guess I don't have anything else to do, so I'll keep you company for a while.
102120.mission_complete: What, you don't even want your rewards?
102120.main: I don't seem very Hawaiian even though my name is Honolulu? Well gee, my bad...|Helena's always acting so gloomy... You should think of ways to make her smile too, Commander.|I was born with this personality. I don't hate you or anything like that...
102120.feeling5: ... Didn't I tell you they're not this big just because I wanted them to be? Well, if you like them that much... then maybe they're not so bad...
102120.upgrade: I didn't really ask you for this...
102120.unlock: Brooklyn-class, Honolulu, reporting in. Hey, listen... could you stop staring at me like that? It's not like they're this big because I wanted them to be...
102120.feeling4: I don't really have anything going for me outside of my body, but you're still being so nice to me... Do you like my body THAT much? Even if you don't, it's not like I... No, I'll stop myself right there, because otherwise you'll just get carried away.
102120.feeling1: So that's who you are, huh, Commander?
102120.propose: This is really embarrassing, so could we just get this over with... Y-you can do whatever you want when it's just the two of us...
102120.drop_descrip: Brooklyn-class Light Cruiser – Honolulu, Hull Number CL-48!
102120.skill: This time things should go well...!
102120.profile: I'm Honolulu of the Brooklyn-class. I've basically only ever served in the Pacific. I was damaged pretty bad once, but somehow I managed to make it... At least I was luckier than Helena...
102120.touch2: *Sigh*... If you're gonna be this direct then I don't even feel like getting mad at you...
102120.mission: If you have the time to stare at me, how about you go finish your remaining missions?
102120.home: Good work. What, are you not satisfied until I say something mean?
102120.expedition: What are you waiting for... A commission's been completed!
102120.mail: Here, mail for you. What? I can at least do something this simple for you...
102120.feeling3: I think people are jealous of me because mine are bigger than theirs… But personally I wish they were smaller. When they're big, you know, it's pretty inconvenient...
102120.lose: I don't want to go to Mare Island again...

101390.detail: Commander, please let me know if there's anything you need me for.
101390.touch: Uhh... the black smoke coming from that side of the kitchen? Ahaha... ha... I have no idea what you're talking about~
101390.login: Commander, have you eaten? Should I prepare something for you?
101390.battle: I have to work hard for Commander today as well~
101390.feeling2: Commander, what are your interests? My hobby is cooking - though sometimes weird stuff come out, it usually tastes pretty good anyway. Mhm!
101390.headtouch: Being treated like a kid... feels a bit weird... ahaha...
101390.mission_complete: Mission rewards, huh... Should I also prepare something for you, Commander?
101390.main: Aww... I thought I followed the recipe perfectly, so how did it turn out like this...? |Commander, make sure to strike the right balance between work and leisure! It's not good to be lazy or overworked~ |Commander, do your best! Believe in yourself, you're the greatest!
101390.feeling5: You feel bad for always imposing on me? It's fine, it's fine! I'm happiest when I can be of use to the one I care about~ so feel free to rely on me even more from now on!
101390.upgrade: Ah! An inspiration for my new recipe!
101390.unlock: Hello Commander, I am the Fletcher-class destroyer, Mullany. From today onwards, we'll be spending a lot of time together. Please take good care of me!
101390.feeling4: Commander, are you keeping up with your schedule? If you feel like you can't manage everything alone, please let me handle your domestic affairs~
101390.feeling1: Cooking for someone you don't like is suffering...
101390.propose: Commander, would you like me to keep cooking for you every day, even after a long, long time? Hm, you'd like there to be fewer weird dishes? Hehe, I guess I can manage that~
101390.profile: The Fletcher-class is pretty big, so it's not strange that you haven't heard of me. Though I had my fair share of dangerous moments, I managed to return peacefully. Right after that, I even went to live the Dragon Empery for a while! Is that why you think I look a bit bigger? Who knows~
101390.touch2: C-Commander... so you're also interested in the racy stuff...
101390.mission: Work hard to finish your missions, Commander~
101390.home: Commander, good work~ Would you like to have a meal? I kept your food warm.
101390.win_mvp: I'm number one? Um... as long as I can be of help to you, I'll be happy...
101390.expedition: Commander, a commission has been finished!
couple_encourage: Fletcher, I'm coming to help you!
101390.mail: Commander, there's mail for you. Don't forget to read it!
101390.feeling3: My cooking would be perfect if I stopped trying to study weird things? Well, that's a darn shame! If you ask me, the element of surprise is the most important spice!

102142.detail: This set really is expertly made. It shocked me when I first laid eyes on it.
102142.touch: No thanks. I can get down on my own. The set isn't a hard climb or anything, I'm just not used to wearing this dress.
102142.login: "Welcome back, darling." ...This feels wrong. Doesn't fit the scene.
102142.main: I'm only wearing this dress because big sis told me to. It's the total opposite of the clothes I'm used to wearing... Hm? That's not the point of this all?|Change my pose? Okay. How's this? ...I have no clue what you think is so funny about this. Guess it doesn't matter as long as big sis is enjoying herself...|Wanna sit next to me? This thing is built to handle several people.
102142.unlock: As unreliable as you are, I didn't think you'd be too scared to approach a movie prop... You're just "admiring it from a distance?" ...Fair enough.
102142.drop_descrip: As unreliable as you are, I didn't think you'd be too scared to approach a movie prop... You're just "admiring it from a distance?" ...Fair enough.
102142.touch2: Are you that keen to taste the power of darkness?
102142.home: Time to go back to the party? All right. Give me a moment to come down.
102142.win_mvp: "Kneel to the power of darkness!" ...Is it cooler to recite this line from the script?

101311.detail: I need to control my sleepiness when treating people on the battlefield. *Yawn*... I'm working on it...
101311.login: Medical staff are valuable and should stay in the back... Frontline duty? That stuff is Vestal's job...
101311.main: This syringe contains Radford's sweetie candy... It won't hurt... You won't feel a thing...|You don't feel so good, do you? Don't worry about me, just stay in bed and rest...|Some of my patients can be pretty problematic... That's when I just dump them on Vestal...
101311.unlock: I love doing relief missions as a nurse... I don't need to go outside or take part in any training, I just need to look after injured people... What about treating them? No worries, they just need to rest and they'll get better.
101311.drop_descrip: I love doing relief missions as a nurse... I don't need to go outside or take part in any training, I just need to look after injured people... What about treating them? No worries, they just need to rest and they'll get better.
101311.touch2: You must have suddenly gotten very sick...

202191.detail: There are always interesting things happening here at the port. I can feel my quiet, ordinary life slipping farther and farther away... Of course, that's not to say this lifestyle is all that bad.
202191.touch: It's what it is... But if you keep at this, my outfit is going to get ruined...
202191.login: I've prepared a barley tea for you today. Now then, steel yourself, and give the day's work all you've got.
202191.main: Do we have time to call up my sisters to join us for some teppanyaki?|It's nice I can push all the maid work onto my sisters, but spending the whole day reading a book by myself is a tad dull...|I've heard summertime is when you see a certain type of rose blooming... But I'm not sure if our port has that particular rose?
202191.unlock: This outfit makes me stand out a bit too much... But, as long as it makes you happy, I'm just as pleased.
202191.drop_descrip: This outfit makes me stand out a bit too much... But, as long as it makes you happy, I'm just as pleased.
202191.touch2: If it's the outfit you're interested in... Sigh... I suppose it's too late to stop you at this point?
202191.home: Are you tired after all that...? Then let me service you with a powerful healing hug.

205062.touch: Why are you staring at me? I'm... suave? Hehe, I suppose I should take that as a compliment.
205062.mission_complete: You're still hammering away at those missions even during the New Year? You sure are hard-working, Commander.
205062.main: Commander, are you cold? You can borrow my coat if you'd like. Ah, don't worry about me, I'm fine. |Learning about the customs of the other nations is quite interesting. I feel like I get along better with the Sakura girls now. |I miss my black tea a bit, but I suppose "when in Rome, do as the Romans do." I guess I should fully enjoy the culture of the Sakura Empire.
205062.feeling5: To be able to experience a new culture like this, and spend the New Year peacefully... is like a dream come true. Commander, it's all thanks to you. As expected of the one I chose.
205062.unlock: I've been wearing Royal attire my whole life, so a change in pace doesn't seem bad. Oh, Commander, good timing. Can you explain to me how to celebrate the New Year here?
205062.drop_descrip: I've been wearing Royal attire my whole life, so a change in pace doesn't seem bad. Oh, Commander, good timing. Can you explain to me how to celebrate the New Year here?
205062.expedition: Since it's the New Year, it would be sad if there was nobody to greet the girls returning from commissions. Don't you think so, Commander?

905011.detail: I'm more willing to listen to Dunkerque than a lot of others. She's a lot more in touch with the masses.
905011.touch: Cheers... Hmph. I never asked for the "blessing" of being someone's sister, but I've already gotten used to what that entails.
905011.login: You... look awfully bored, Commander. Hmph, what a coincidence. That makes two of us.
905011.mission_complete: C'mon, put all that stuff aside and have a drink with me.
905011.main: Letting go of everything and losing yourself to the merriment of song and dance... that is what a banquet should be about. Not this pompous farce that makes even wine taste bad. |The one thing that this banquet has going for it is the fact that everyone's smiles are genuine and heartfelt... Look, I'm praising you, can't you tell? |Commander, I'm not going to exchange pleasantries with you. C'mon, it's not like we just met for the first time, right?
905011.feeling5: I loathe red tape, nor do I have any desire to stand here like a flower vase for people to stare at... But I'm doing all of this for you, because you make me feel like it's all worth it. You've committed quite the serious offense, mon amour...
905011.unlock: The guest of honor shouldn't be wandering around looking for girls drinking alone... Hmph, might as well have a drink while you're here anyway.
905011.drop_descrip: The guest of honor shouldn't be wandering around looking for girls drinking alone... Hmph, might as well have a drink while you're here anyway.
905011.mission: You still have missions to do even now? ... Need my help?
905011.home: Did you just come back from battle? Here, cheers.
905011.win_mvp: Mmm... the wind on the battlefield... now that's what I'm used to.
905011.expedition: A commission fleet has returned? Let's head down to greet them together then. I needed some fresh air anyway.
905011.lose: Hmph. Still better than going to that banquet...

10500011.detail: Since I went through all the effort of putting a swimsuit on, why don't we head down into the water? Woahh... that's not what I meant! I just wanted to help out a little with the exercises…
10500011.login: It's not a trip to the ocean without... swimsuits! The summery, slightly liberated version of Fubuki is here~!
10500011.main: *stare*... Commander, are you ogling me...? That's no good!|I see a lot of my friends in swimsuits as well. Looks like over here, you can play on the beach all year long.|It's a little embarrassing.. so please stop staring at me so much.
10500011.feeling5: I'm okay with putting on my swimsuit and going out with you every once in a while, Commander, as a special treat. But only sometimes.
10500011.unlock: Tada~! It's your favorite Shirakami Fubuki, Hololive Summer version! Commander, pleased to be your fox!
10500011.drop_descrip: Tada~! It's your favorite Shirakami Fubuki, Hololive Summer version! Commander, pleased to be your fox!
10500011.touch2: You're not allowed to touch right there either!

900002.touch: 指挥官，来一杯？黑啤不会苦的，试试吧？|走，打一盘，我会让着你的！|指挥官，请下达指令！我的舰炮已经饥渴难耐了……

10500021.detail: Beach volleyball...? I wonder if I can do it... You sure you don't want to 1v1 me with a horror game instead?
10500021.login: Welcome back, Commander~ Would you like to relax on the beach again today?
10500021.main: My buddy "Monkfish liver" came with me~|Commander, I did my best to make you a lunchbox, but... how does it taste?|*Staaare* If it's a staring contest with Commander, there's no way I'll lose!
10500021.unlock: "Hello, my friends! I hope you're well~! This is Sora, on site at a beach in a slightly different world!" Beach visits just feel so invigorating, don't they? On another note, I can't swim...
10500021.drop_descrip: "Hello, my friends! I hope you're well~! This is Sora, on site at a beach in a slightly different world!" Beach visits just feel so invigorating, don't they? On another note, I can't swim…
10500021.touch2: To think that Commander would do something like that to me... You're naughty! Bad Commander!

900003.touch: 指挥官！~你呀，本来可以做得更好的，但为什么总是正经不起来呢……|镇守府一直这样毫无改变，指挥官你至少努力点啊！|指挥官？到底有没有认真听我说话呀？我要用粉笔头砸你了~~最讨厌别人问话不回了~哼！

10500031.detail: I-I'm telling you just this once, so... I sink like a rock in the water, so make sure you support me properly, okay! I'm okay with shallow water, though.
10500031.touch: You wanna play a game with me? I'm super duper strong, so prepare yourself!
10500031.login: Whew~ I'm glad I didn't sleep in today. Well, what should I do, Commander?
10500031.main: Mas... Commander! It's really confuzzling because I'm not used to calling people that ...|Just because I'm a virtual maid doesn't mean that I'm good at doing all sorts of chores!|In exchange for taking care of chores, feed me tasty sushi~!|Hehehehe, I'll be able to make my broadcast more interesting if I upgrade my equipment! For now, let's set the visual effects to MAX, start this up like so, and ... let's blow everything up!!! ... Eh, an error...? ... Come onNNNNNNNN!!!
10500031.feeling5: Commander, are you interested in live streaming too? Yaaay! Then, for your debut as a newbie streamer, pick between a 24-hour endurance stream and Tetris 99, and let's get streaming~
10500031.unlock: Commander, good Aquafternoon~! Nice to meet you, it's Aqua, the Gamer Maid from Hololive! I'll show ya what the strongest maid can do!
10500031.drop_descrip: Commander, good Aquafternoon~! Nice to meet you, it's Aqua, the Gamer Maid from Hololive! I'll show ya what the strongest maid can do!
10500031.mission: M... Mission? ...To tell you the truth, I've got a disease that kills me if I leave the room! As such, I'll leave the Mission to YOU, Commander!!!
