10500031.lose: *Breathes in* ...Eh, did I just black out?

207032.detail: I always feel my heart racing when I wear a different outfit in front of you, Commander~
207032.touch: Did you want to talk, Commander? I'll always be here to listen to you~
207032.login: Good day, Commander. Are you ready to attend the ball?
207032.main: As dance partners, we should hold hands like this... Commander, can you feel my warmth? |nil|The orchestra has started playing~ Commander, would you like to dance with me?
207032.unlock: An invitation to the ball? Hehe, I would be honored to go... as long as you don't decline, Commander~
207032.drop_descrip: An invitation to the ball? Hehe, I would be honored to go... as long as you don't decline, Commander~
207032.touch2: Commander, being proud about doing something inappropriate doesn't make it any less inappropriate.

301600.touch: General, give me a piggyback ride! We must charge into the enemy stronghold!
301600.login: General! It's time to charge into battle!
301600.battle: I will lead the charge into batt... Hey, stop! Wait for me!
301600.feeling2: How I know so much? Urakaze-sama taught me everything about the warring states! She's really smart! But Hamakaze is still my best friend in the end! Heheheh~
301600.mission_complete: General, our mission rewards are here! How much koku did we receive?
301600.main: General! Come play warring states with me! You can be... Ieyasu! I'll be Mitsunari!|Hamakaze! Tanikaze! Let's depart! We're heading for the capital!|Urakaze-sama, my coat has been torn again... Fix it for me!
301600.feeling5: General, Urakaze-sama seemed angry at me and said I've started being cold to Hamakaze! But I still want to play with you... So come on! Let's go play together with Hamakaze!
301600.upgrade: I am Isokaze, the leader of Destroyer Division 17!
301600.unlock: All units, attaaack! ...Wait a second, where am I?! Oh, I know you! Urakaze-sama said you're... the general! Hmph! I'm Isokaze, the one destined to become a general that will make the whole world tremble in fear!
301600.feeling4: General, let's play a game! Huh?! You've got work to do?! You really do? Do you want me to help? Then how about a massage? ...Hooray! I love you, General!
301600.feeling1: Hmph! I'm done playing with you! Hamakaze, Tanikaze, where are you?
301600.propose: General, if anyone starts being mean to you then tell me. Hamakaze and I will go and get revenge on them for you. We're here for you, because we're all friends!
301600.profile: I am Isokaze of DD17! In the past, you see, I've worked with Hamakaze, Urakaze, Tanikaze... oh, and Yukikaze! My service record stands second to none! And that's why you should put me in charge of your missions!
301600.mission: General! Put me in charge of the mission! I'll finish it you before you can say "set sail"!
301600.home: You make me proud, General! Hey, uh, listen! I have a report for you! You see...
301600.win_mvp: Urakaze-sama, can you see my glorious victory?!
301600.expedition: Our target: the base's docks! We must welcome back the commission team! Giddy-up, General!
couple_encourage: Hamakaze, follow my lead!
301600.mail: General, I have a letter for you!
301600.feeling3: Western Army, attack! Fire on the Eastern Army! Our next move will be... Oh no! Hideaki was lured away! That's unfair, General! Darn, now I'm... *Sob*...
301600.lose: Hamakaze, Hamakaze where are you... You have to save me!

202083.detail: Don't worry, I've hidden my gun. If anything happens, I will protect you.
202083.touch: You'd like to escort me? Normally, I'd decline because that'd be embarrassing, but... you'd look so wretched that I simply have no choice but to accept.
202083.login: There is no need for panic, Master. I've become quite accustomed to your lack of punctuality.
202083.main: Making your maid be your partner is a difficult request that falls outside normal lines of business. As fair compensation, please bring me a cake later.|As your partner, I will naturally draw plenty of unwanted attention. I must steel myself mentally.|I can see other members of the Maid Team going about their business... What a strange fetish you have, Master, to make someone who should be working behind the scenes take center stage...
202083.unlock: The fact that you're asking your own maid to be your partner at the ball shows a concerning lack of gumption as a human being... However, if you go and make a fool of yourself, it will reflect poorly upon my standing as a maid. Therefore, I have no choice but to accompany you.
202083.drop_descrip: The fact that you're asking your own maid to be your partner at the ball shows a concerning lack of gumption as a human being... However, if you go and make a fool of yourself, it will reflect poorly upon my standing as a maid. Therefore, I have no choice but to accompany you.
202083.touch2: Master, please do not get carried away in your excitement.
202083.home: Master, I do hope you haven't forgotten that there is still a party to attend... How hopeless you are. Allow me to tidy up your appearance.
202083.expedition: Your enthusiasm for this party is understandable, but please do not forget about the commissions.

101392.detail: After studying abroad in the Dragon Empery and being exposed to their history and culture, I've learned to be a bit calmer. However, I'm still the same person as before... as you can probably tell from my cooking...
101392.touch: The elegance of ladies from the Empery, walking with their parasols opened, is a sight to behold. So, I picked up a few things from them - want to see?
101392.login: Would you like to have some soup dumplings?
101392.headtouch: Commander, are you... interested in my new hairstyle?
101392.feeling5: Cooking for someone else... is a whole different experience. Cooking for you? Hm, I'd say that's a bit of a heart-racing sensation, hehe~
101392.unlock: What's with the weird look, Commander? Ah, I got this outfit while studying abroad in the Dragon Empery. Umm... does it suit me?
101392.drop_descrip: What's with the weird look, Commander? Ah, I got this outfit while studying abroad in the Dragon Empery. Umm... does it suit me?
101392.mission: Today's business is best done today, Commander.
101392.win_mvp: The things I learned in the Dragon Empery came in handy.

101351.detail: When it comes to bikes... I don't know squat! So I just got my Royal Navy pal to help out! I've gotta thank her later!
101351.touch: Aha! You're digging my bike and style, aren't you, Commander? Aren't you jelly? Since I'm so nice, I'll let you stare until you're satisfied!
101351.login: Hmm? Hmmmmmm? Man, you look miserable, Commander! Sit here and I'll take you on a wild ride! Ahahahaha!
101351.main: Still looking brand new? Well yeah, thanks to my daily pro-level maintenance!|You wanna ride my bike? Of course you... can't! Think what'd happen if you crash it!|If there's somewhere you wanna go, if you ask me really nicely with a cherry on top, I just might let you hop on~
101351.unlock: Ahaha~! Are you seeing this, Commander? This sturdiness, this gorgeous paint job, and these special accessories hand-picked by yours truly! Muahaha! I am the true speed-star of this port!
101351.drop_descrip: Ahaha~! Are you seeing this, Commander? This sturdiness, this gorgeous paint job, and these special accessories hand-picked by yours truly! Muahaha! I am the true speed-star of this port!
101351.touch2: Seizing the chance to feel me up, huh~? You dirty perv~
101351.home: Speed-star, engine at full throttle! Let's roll! ... Teehee~ I came up with that sweet catchphrase long ago!

408010.detail: Booooom! Did I scare ya there, Commander?
408010.touch: Bombers?! Aaaahhhh! Commander, there are some things you just can't joke about!
408010.login: So you're finally back, huh. I thought I was gonna die of boredom.
408010.hp_warning: Dammit... I'm gonna have to dive real deep...
408010.feeling2: Heheh, I love hide-and-seek! It's also my specialty!
408010.mission_complete: The mission rewards are here! If you don't want 'em then I'll just help myself!
408010.main: I'm gonna go check around the office for places to hide. Hehehe...|Adjust firing parameters... check the compass and scales... Clank, clunk... *Giggle*...|How about a game of hide-and-seek, Commander?
408010.feeling5: I just realized something big. That your bed is ridiculously warm! I'm gonna sleep with you from now o... What? Did I say something strange?
408010.upgrade: Feels like I've gotten more dexterous!
408010.unlock: Heheh, now I too have a commander! I'm U-81, I love playing hide-and-seek. If you can't find me, just shout "U-81, I admit defeat!" and I'll probably come out of hiding.
408010.feeling4: Hmm? Found me again, huh. You've been finding me a lot lately...
408010.propose: This... must be what "getting hitched" means! Hehehe~ I'm happy, but also kinda embarrassed... O-of course, I love you very much, Commander!
408010.drop_descrip: Iron Blood Type VIIC submarine – U-81.
408010.profile: I'm U-81, Type VIIC submarine of the Iron Blood Navy. I have a ton of sisters who can be pretty unruly sometimes! ... Also, I have the sinking of Ark Royal under my belt! She's a weird woman... I can't properly explain what makes her weird, though...
408010.touch2: Whoah?! I warned you about doing that, Commander! My torpedoes almost just went off...
408010.mission: Commander, you've got a new mission.
408010.home: Here's a towel, Commander. Wipe that sweat off.
408010.win_mvp: Now you know the power of U-boats!
408010.expedition: Hmm? Commission team's back. Mind if I go greet 'em? I could use a quick dip in the harbor.
408010.mail: Isn't it nice having a letter waiting for you when you come back to port~?
408010.feeling3: Not to brag, but I have a pretty stunning service record. Go on, let me hear your applause!
408010.lose: Damn... The Commander will avenge me for this!

107031.detail: Commander...? Thank you for before. As an Eagle Union carrier, I shouldn't be feeling down after losing in beach volleyball! ...Yep! Saratoga, launching again!
107031.touch: In beach volleyball...I l-lost to destroyers... my sister isn't here... Commander, can I cry on your shoulder for a while?
107031.login: Commander, let's head to the beach today! I want to eat chilled watermelon!
107031.mission_complete: Commander, are you done with the mission? I'm tired from volleyball practice as well. Phew... It's so hot I'm too worn to prank...
107031.main: When you talk about a sport to play on the beach, it has to be this!|Commander, how about we get into the sea? I'll borrow you my lifesaver!|W-Wales? Why are you hugging me suddenly... I've grown 'bigger'? Really? That's right! I have grown bigger after all!
107031.upgrade: If I evolve once more, I'm gonna show the Royals what I'm made of!
107031.unlock: Even in a day off, I'm not loosening up! Phew... Swimsuit, check. All preparations complete! Launch time! I'll show you Sister Sara's power!
107031.drop_descrip: Even if we don't get to relax on holiday, it's always good to have a swimsuit! Ok, let's go! Are you ready to swim?
107031.touch2: Commander! Saratoga won! Come and see! I beat Honolulu! She can't believe it!
107031.mission: Eat the ice cream, and go complete the mission! I'll prepare a fireworks show for tonight!
107031.home: We~ are back~ Phew~ it's so hot!
107031.expedition: The girls out for commission have returned. I made some shaved ice with my planes. Commander, want some syrup on top?

207029.detail: Everyone has something dear they wouldn't give up for the world. Whatever yours may be, Commander, allow me to protect it with you!
207029.touch: As long as I have your support, I can brave the battlefield without reserve!
207029.login: At last you're here, Commander! Assign me any missions you need done!
207029.main: My Swordfish squadrons are in tip-top condition today! Likewise for my Fulmar squadrons!|It is customarily destroyers that protect carriers, but there's nothing wrong with reversing that. Don't you agree?|To protect what's close to you, you must always keep a watchful eye on the horizon. I trust you to do that, Commander.
207029.unlock: Ark Royal retrofitting complete! Now I can protect you, my friends, and of course, the little destroyers, to the very end!
207029.drop_descrip: Ark Royal retrofitting complete! Now I can protect you, my friends, and of course, the little destroyers, to the very end!
207029.touch2: Commander...? Excuse me, but what's gotten into you?!
207029.home: I need to go check on the destroyers! I'll be right back, Commander!

402050.detail: Why are you here by yourself, Commander? ...W-were you perhaps waiting for everyone else to leave...?! Oh, you weren't?
402050.touch: Are... are you trying to condition me to be less cautious by touching me...?!
402050.login: It is time to begin working. C-Commander, please give it your all...!
402050.battle: Everyone, p-please exercise your own judgment...?
402050.feeling2: I wonder if Leipzig fell down somewhere... Commander, let's go look for her... I mean, would you like to come with me?
402050.headtouch: Eek?! Suddenly touching my head like that... Commander, you're thinking of doing something weird, aren't you...?! Am, am I wrong?
402050.mission_complete: Did you finish all your missions? As expected of the commander...
402050.main: Commander, do you like Brötchen? I see... Th-then, if work goes well, I... I'll make some for you!|I wonder if there's anything that can be done about Leipzig always collapsing... Ph-physical exercises, you say? Commander, are you planning to do something weird to Leipzig?!|Am I being too hard on you? What should I do... If I was to make you upset with me... W-well, I'm sure it's fine, since you're probably thinking up all kinds of weird things right now...!
402050.feeling5: Now that I think about it more, Commander, you haven't tried doing anything weird to me. If anything, you've treated me really nicely and it's somehow reassuring to be with you... Even if you tried to have your way with me, I don't think I'd... Wh-wh-wh-what am I saying?! P-please forget I ever said anything...!
402050.upgrade: I hope all this hard work pays off...
402050.unlock: I am the second ship of the Leipzig-class, Nürnberg. Starting today, I shall serve you to the best of my abilities... Is that acceptable?
402050.feeling4: Commander, we've been spending more and more time together recently... Ugh, you really were planning something weird after all... At this rate, I... I'll be... Fine with it...?
402050.propose: I, I know already... I'll do whatever you say... so please don't look at me! It's embarrassing... So embarrassing that it's driving me crazy... I, I wish this would end already! ...Hauu...
402050.profile: Though I received many modifications during the war, I never was able to put any of it to good use... But, there aren't many ships in the Iron Blood with longer service histories than me? I, I can't even believe it myself...
402050.touch2: Aaah?! Wh-what are you doing all of a sudden, Commander?!
402050.mission: There's a new mission, Commander. Did you get the previous one sorted out yet?
402050.home: I know you're tired from your sortie, Commander, but please hang in there a bit longer for everyone else's sake... I mean, if you could...
402050.win_mvp: Huh? I'm number one? That's rather... unexpected, isn't it?
402050.expedition: A commission has been completed. You should know what to do without me reminding you, right?
couple_encourage: Let's focus on the fight!
402050.mail: You have new mail, Commander. I hope it's not a glitter bomb...
402050.feeling3: You want me to teach you how to make Brötchen? I don't mind, but I must warn you that I have high standards... Wait, are you perhaps using this as an excuse to get closer to me...?!
402050.lose: How could this happen... It surely must've been my fault... I'm so sorry...

301601.detail: General, I want my red envelope!
301601.touch: Huh? General, I'm not cold~ Ahaha, stop rubbing my belly, it tickles!
301601.mission_complete: General, what are these? New Year's presents?
301601.main: Woah! It's snowing! General, let's call everyone out and have a snowball fight! |Why is everyone so sluggish during the winter? I think playing in the snow is suuuuper fun! |General, General, look! It's a tiger! Rooooaarrr! Ahahaha~
301601.feeling5: General, General! Make sure to wake me up for the New Year's shrine visit! Even if I sleep in, make sure to come get me! This year, we definitely need to go together!
301601.unlock: General, General, look! It's my New Year's outfit! Urakaze made it for me! Let's play a bunch of Sengoku wargames this year as well!
301601.drop_descrip: General, General, look! It's my New Year's outfit! Urakaze made it for me! Let's play a bunch of Sengoku wargames this year as well!

100000.detail: Buli? Buli? Where are we? What are we gonna do here?
100000.touch: Buli? Do you want to be bulified?
100000.login: If I swing this wrench hard enough, I could poke a hole in the office floor, buli!
100000.battle: I don't know what I'm doing, but I'm doing it, buli!
100000.feeling2: My big sis can apparently only strengthen one color. I can strengthen a bunch! Which means... that I'm more powerful than her? Wow! I'm stronger than her, buli!
100000.mission_complete: Rewards... Can I eat them, buli?
100000.main: Us Bulins are pretty awesome, buli!|Is there nothing for Bulin to do? Really? Then let's go play! Wheee!|Commander, let's go dig for some treasure, buli~!
100000.feeling5: My heart races whenever I see you, Commander! I could dismantle the entire dock for you! Could this be... my inner fire? Buli!
100000.unlock: Buli? Seems like I can help make your fleet stronger, buli!
100000.feeling4: I'm not meant for combat, yet you use me anyway, so being the more sensible Bulin, I need to thank you! I guess it's just because we're too cute...? *Kyah~* I might be in love~!
100000.feeling1: Wahh~! Commander is a big, big dummy!
100000.propose: Bulin has been caught~ Ahh, I'm blushing so much! What will I do! Let's buy some new toys and celebrate!
100000.drop_descrip: Universal Bulin. Can be used to limit break all ships of Elite rarity or below.
100000.skill: My wrench is the wrench that will pierce the earth!
100000.profile: They say I'm just like my sister, but we're actually in charge of different colors... What's a color? Sounds yummy!
100000.home: Buli! Look, I'm full of energy!
100000.win_mvp: Buli? Could it be that... I'm super strong?!
couple_encourage: Sis, what are you bulin here?
100000.mail: Something strange just popped outta me, buli...
100000.feeling3: Bulin is happy that she can help everyone get stronger, but she enjoys playing with you too, Commander! Bulin can help strengthen you... Aww, why not?
100000.lose: Huh? Am I... no good in battle, buli?

431230.detail: I'm SO returning these kitties to Akashi... Although, I'd feel really guilty if I did that... Ugh, what's a girl to do...
431230.touch: Commander, would you like something to drink?
431230.login: How tiring... I should go take a break now. I'll have to check if Z26 and the others did their homework later...
431230.main: Hey, Z28! Stop treating the Meowfficers like pets! Look, I know they seem like pets in more ways than one!|Javelin and her friends aren't too keen about coffee. Heh, that proves that they're still just kids.|So that's where you're hiding! Gotcha! ...What? I'm totally not wasting time playing hide-and-seek with the U-boats!
431230.unlock: *sigh*... Taking care of Meowfficers is more work than you'd think... They're awfully needy for support units. Commander, make absolute sure you don't turn out like them.
431230.drop_descrip: *sigh*... Taking care of Meowfficers is more work than you'd think... They're awfully needy for support units. Commander, make absolute sure you don't turn out like them.
431230.touch2: Wh-what are you trying to do?!
431230.home: Don't forget to keep your dorms nice and stocked up... Just like these kitties...
431230.win_mvp: Whether in battles or in missions or in studies, diligence begets success!

306031.touch: Hehe... Master, if your heart races, then it's my victory~
306031.main: At least for tonight, I wish you and I to pursue the happiness of being together... |nil|Master, what do you think of your Tanabata present? Are~ you~ satisfied~?
306031.unlock: While everyone slips into sweet dreams from the night's festivities, the sound of gossamer sliding off of smooth skin reaches your ears... Hehe, would you like to spend this night under the stars with me, Master~?
306031.drop_descrip: While everyone slips into sweet dreams from the night's festivities, the sound of gossamer sliding off of smooth skin reaches your ears... Hehe, would you like to spend this night under the stars with me, Master~?
306031.touch2: The ephemeral autumn is but a fleeting dream

301842.detail: These markings are the proof of my battle scars as a warrior... they're not just doodles! Ugh... I swear, I'll be back for revenge after I train some more!
301842.touch: Commander, make sure the matches continue smoothly!
301842.main: Aaahhhhh!! Jean Bart, you don't have to shank every shuttlecock out of existence!|Pooky, I got some sunflower seeds from Hanazuki! Here, come and eat your fill~ Grow big and strong and scare the heck out of the commander~ Ahaha!|I can't sit still during the New Year! After all, there are so many things going on that only happen during this time of year!
301842.unlock: I, Akizuki-class destroyer, Suzutsuki, shall not allow you to pass through these arches! Hwuh?! I missed the return again...!
301842.drop_descrip: I, Akizuki-class destroyer, Suzutsuki, shall not allow you to pass through these arches! Hwuh?! I missed the return again...!
301842.expedition: The girls from the commission fleet are back! Darn it, I wish Hatsushimo could come with me!
301842.mail: Suzutsuki, now reading the contents of your mail out loud!

608010.detail: Wh-why are you looking at me...?
608010.touch: Mine don't hold a candle to the massive mounds of some other girls... Hehe, hehehe... Sorry if that disappoints you, Commander...
608010.login: Ehh?! C-could you not pop in out of the blue like that... It scares me...
608010.battle: Do whatever, it doesn't matter, I just wanna get this over with quick...
608010.hp_warning: I wanna get out of the water...
608010.feeling2: Like I said, don't worry about me... I'm right here, out of sight, out of mind... Hehehehe...
608010.mission_complete: Leave the mission rewards alone for too long and shrooms might start growing on them... Hehe, hehehehe...
608010.main: You're awful busy today, Commander... You want my help? Umm... I-I'll think about it...|It's safe and quiet under the surface... I'd love to have you down there with me... Hehe, hehehehe...|Could you... c-close the curtains, please? The sunlight... it burns...
608010.feeling5: I'm glad I have somone as d-diligent and charitable like you to count on... Hehehe... Y-you want me to give you a hand sometimes? I-I'll try...
608010.upgrade: My guns could use an upgrade too...
608010.unlock: You've gotta be the commander... My name is T-Torricelli, here to claim this room for myself... Don't worry about me, I'll just be sitting in some quiet corner... Hehe, hehehehe...
608010.feeling4: Commander, can I come a step c-closer? Hehe, hehehehe... Your hand feels so nice and warm... Hehe...
608010.feeling1: You're even edgier than I am... Hehehe...
608010.propose: Hehe, hehehe... Now you're obliged to provide for me forever... That was j-just a joke... So, what comes next...?
608010.profile: I'm Brin-class submarine Torricelli... Just remember my name, and I'll be happy... My battle with the Royal Navy? It taught me a lesson about what happens when you underestimate your enemies... Hehehehe...
608010.touch2: I guess this means I've c-caught your interest...
608010.mission: Missions? Ugh, I hate missions... Could we just pretend they don't exist...
608010.home: I know this scent... When I smell it, it means you've come b-back... Hehe, hehehehe...
608010.win_mvp: Can I come up now? Okay, I-I'm heading back now... Hehe, hehehehe...
608010.expedition: The commission team's back? I couldn't care less... You're gonna go see them? I-I'll tag along then...
couple_encourage: Your personality is my k-kryptonite...
I'm not sure we're on the same wavelength...
608010.mail: There's mail for you. I've made sure nobody's read it but me... Hehe, hehehe...
608010.feeling3: Yuubari said thanks? I just gave her an idea for a c-cannon modification, that's all... Now she wants my help with it, too? Uhh, I'm gonna pass...

900240.detail: Will you still come see me even if I grow out of this body?
900240.login: Did you have a good rest, Commander? I'm full of energy. Probably.
900240.hp_warning: This isn't good enough... I used to be much better...
900240.feeling2: *Yawns* Commander, want to take a nap with me?
900240.feeling5: I've been thinking... If you'd been there back then, I might have been able to take down {namecode:71}... But if she comes after you now, then this time I won't let her go...
900240.upgrade: Mm... Back to sleep for me...
900240.unlock: Benson-class destroyer, Laffey, awaiting your orders... Commander, these ears aren't real... you don't need to stare at them...
900240.feeling4: I'm used to being alone... But I think I like it better when you're with me, Commander... Mmm... Zzzzzz...
900240.propose: I thought I wouldn't mind becoming a demon again if it was for you, Commander… But since you've taken such good care of me, I guess my chance for that is gone… Have I disappointed you, Commander?
900240.drop_descrip: Benson-class destroyer - Laffey, Hull Number DD-459!
900240.profile: I'm the much anticipated Benson-class destroyer, Laffey, who performed excellently during the Third Battle of the Solomon Sea. Battleship? What's that?
900240.mission: Looks like we've still got a few missions to do...
900240.home: I've returned from the mission. Regrouping with original unit.
900240.expedition: I was actually wondering whether you'd remember it or not, but a commission has been completed, Commander.
couple_encourage: There's no point pretending to be tough...
Kaede's Legion, attack!
900240.feeling3: I thought you were a bit boring at first, Commander... But now that I've been thinking about it, I'm not really motivated about anything other than fighting, so we might be a decent match...
900240.lose: Mmm... We lost... They weren't so easy were they?

102131.main: How I wish I could bring this chair with me on sorties... Helena, could you help upgrade my rigging?|I am Lucky Lou. I may not look like it, but I actually have experience with fortune-telling.|Brr... It's actually a bit cold... Commander, could you come a little closer and... share your body heat with me?
102131.unlock: What do you think of this foreign dress, Commander? *Giggle* ...Perhaps it's rekindled something within you?
102131.drop_descrip: What do you think of this foreign dress, Commander? *Giggle* ...Perhaps it's rekindled something within you?
102131.touch2: Oh, do you mean I've put it on wrong? Have I really...?

802010.detail: I love dancing because it brings joy to people♪
802010.touch: Are you worn out, Commander? Shall I perform my energizing dance for you?
802010.login: Bonjour~ Commander, before we get to work, I say we do some stretches~
802010.battle: Allow me to have this dance~
802010.hp_warning: It seems I'm not in pace with the battlefield...
802010.feeling2: I often hear people say that we of Iris Libre are romantics, but the way I see it, we simply focus on life's little details.
802010.mission_complete: Oh, was that the commission complete notification? You should give it a look, Commander.
802010.main: The Land of Gold – the Sakura Empire! Fantastique! I do hope to see it one day!|Compared to those 2 years at Fort-de-France... it's wonderful to be able to dance freely beneath the blue sky~|Commander, is there anything I can help you with? Whatever it is, I'd love to.
802010.feeling5: The gorgeous radiance of yesterday, the heart-throbbing excitement of today, the overflowing hopes of tomorrow! Every day is so wonderful! Each passing day, my love for you grows even stronger!
802010.upgrade: Ohoh, my steps feel lighter now~
802010.unlock: Bonjour~ I'm Émile Bertin of Iris Libre. You can just call me Émile~ I want to make friends with everyone here~
802010.feeling4: Dancing when one wants to – that is what's known as the courage to express one's love of life. Commander, I believe a romanticist must sometimes show courage and express their feelings in some way. Like this– *Kiss*... What do you believe, Commander?
802010.feeling1: I can't feel any passion coming from you, Commander...
802010.propose: I want to express my feelings in this joyous moment through a dance and a kiss... Commander, could you indulge me?
802010.profile: I'm Émile Bertin of Iris Libre~ In days of old, I worked hard laying mines... and leading destroyers. I also transported gold, took part in Operation Dragoon, and participated in a few other missions, so you could say I got through the war unscathed... I suppose?
802010.touch2: Commander, if you're asking me for a dance, you need to do it more courteously~!
802010.mission: We've been relayed new missions? Then let's get them all done at once♪
802010.home: Commander, if you feel tired then some rest would do you good. Taking breaks is important.
802010.win_mvp: Merci pour tout~ Thank you for your time♪
802010.expedition: Commander, look towards the harbor! The commission team has returned.
802010.feeling3: Because we focus on the details, we can see the beauty of everyday things. I believe a true romanticist values even the smallest of life's beautiful things.
802010.lose: Oh, dear... Perhaps I left my guard too low.

901031.detail: Tartu's not gonna get washed away by a stray wave, I hope... Yeah, figured as much...
901031.touch: Teehee~ Well? How do you like my swimsuit~? Yeah, I know, I'm flat in a few places...
901031.main: Everyone's looking so cute~! Woo~! Hm? I'M looking cute too...? W-woo~!|Isn't it great to just forget about work and have a good time~? But, uh, what's up with that Royal Knight over there? She's casually playing around too, even though she's still on duty...|Beach barbeque! Heck yeah! I'd love to grill some vegetables, but I'd rather someone else does the bell peppers!
901031.unlock: Commandeeer! What are you doing? It's our day off! Turn the work part of your brain off and just have fun! C'mon, let's enjoy ourselves on the beach!
901031.drop_descrip: Commandeeer! What are you doing? It's our day off! Turn the work part of your brain off and just have fun! C'mon, let's enjoy ourselves on the beach!
901031.touch2: I know I don't hold a candle to Tartu, but... Wait, what do you think you're doing?!

306071.detail: I control my carrier-based planes with this charm... A carrier cannot fight a foe face-to-face after all. This katana is merely a last resort.
306071.touch: Hehe... Commander, are you here to enjoy some sweet sake as well? Don't worry, you won't get drunk...
306071.login: Good work, Commander. Please allow me to prepare the hamaya!
306071.battle: Full force ahead for the Commander's victory!
306071.main: The thing about Junyou is... Well, Commander, if something's bothering you, you can consult me, you know? | Because I'm in Shigure's debt, I cook her some food from time to time. She's really a good girl, even if she doesn't always act like one. | Commander, would you like to write an Ema? Even if your wishes don't get fulfilled, it's still great to just be able to write down your thoughts.
306071.unlock: Commander, everyone seems to be busy with end-of-year preparations. If there is anything I can do to help, please let me know.
306071.drop_descrip: Commander, everyone seems to be busy with end-of-year preparations. If there is anything I can do to help, please let me know.
306071.home: You can leave the purification to me if Fusou and Yamashiro are both busy, all right? After all, I happen to be quite knowledgeable about that subject.

101080.detail: Umm... Why are you always watching me do my warm-ups? Do you like watching me sweat?
101080.touch: Are you helping me recover? ... Thank you...
101080.login: Commander, want to do some warm-ups with me?
101080.battle: Lets finish this quick before I get hungry!
101080.feeling2: Commander, is it really okay for you to sit around all day? Get outside and do some sports!
101080.mission_complete: Phew~ I'm exhausted... Save some Oxy-cola for me when the rewards arrive!
101080.main: Commander, want to work out a bit? Sitting for so long is terrible for your body!|I thought we were going for some long distance trip at Wake Island again.|I swear it wasn't my tummy making that noise!
101080.feeling5: Commander, how about going on a jog with me? I want to share the beautiful scenery I find with you.
101080.upgrade: Not enough... I can still go faster...!
101080.unlock: You can just call me Maury. As a track athlete, I hold the Union's speed record, reaching a maximum speed of 42.8 knots. Just don't make me run a marathon...
101080.feeling4: I feel like I can run even farther when I'm next to you, Commander. What an incredible feeling!
101080.feeling1: Sorry, I've got some training to do, so I gotta go!
101080.propose: No matter how fast I run, I can't escape my feelings for you, Commander...
101080.drop_descrip:
Gridley-class destroyer, Maury, Hull Number DD-401
<color=#ffde38>Unlock build after receiving</color>
101080.profile: I'm Maury, the fourth ship of the Gridley-class destroyer squadron. Although I'm the youngest of my class, I'm also the fastest short-distance Union ship! I'm prone to getting hungry a lot? Well, they say that light meals make you live longer, don't they?
101080.touch2: ...!! Hey! There's a line you shouldn't cross when giving massages.
101080.mission: You've still got some missions to finish up, Commander! Put your back into it, it's the final stretch!
101080.home: Rest now so that we can sprint faster later!
101080.win_mvp: Like I said, those guys can't keep up with me!
101080.expedition: I need to get some exercise... Commander, a commission just got completed, so could you send me out on the next one?
101080.mail: You've got new mail. It's about that celebratory party, isn't it?
101080.feeling3: Want me to teach you how to run faster, Commander? There's quite a lot to it, actually.
101080.lose: ... I need to get back before everyone starts worrying about me.

900260.detail: Commander, if you keep looking at me like that, you’ll be eaten up.
900260.login: Justice and righteousness are for the strong only. The weak can only weep in vain.
900260.battle: Entertain me with your final struggles. Hehehe...
900260.hp_warning: It’s time for a death match! Heheh- hehehe!
900260.feeling2: The weak will be eliminated. If you cannot accept that, then simply become stronger.
900260.mission_complete: Here are the rewards, the fruits of your labor.
900260.main: I shall conquer all, no matter who stands against me.|Our enemies may be strong, but that is what makes them worth crushing. Heheh...|The girls of the Fifth Carrier Division? They might amount to something if they work hard enough.
900260.feeling5: I have so much I want to say, but I forget them all the moment I see your face...
900260.upgrade: Not bad. I’ve come up with some new combat techniques.
900260.unlock: Will I be able to find a worthy foe here? Very well. I’m yours. Perhaps this, too, is destiny.
900260.feeling4: I cannot comprehend these emotions... is this some sort of primal instinct?
900260.feeling1: It seems like you're not the hero I was looking for...
900260.propose: ... Is this for me? Hm... perhaps it is fate for the strong to be drawn to each other. If that is the case, I shall follow my instincts then. Hehehe~
900260.skill: Only the strong may survive on the battlefield!
900260.profile: I am {namecode:92}, from the First Carrier Division. I was originally designed to be a battleship, but fate had different plans or me. Enemies? I simply slaughter them, but only because it is my duty, not for fun.
900260.touch2: ... Fine. If you say it helps you relax...
900260.mission: Commander, stop slacking around. There are still missions to complete.
900260.home: A fitting reward for the ears of our enemies. Let us enjoy the spoils of war leisurely.
900260.win_mvp: Such is the fate of the weak. Death, nothing more.
900260.expedition: The girls on commission have returned. Go on ahead, I will prepare some refreshments for them.
couple_encourage: Sister, please take this seriously.
The First Carrier Division is not to be looked down upon!
I did not expect to be fighting alongside you all...
900260.mail: Your mail is here. Try not to forget it next time.
900260.feeling3: Should you be defeated one day, it simply means that you were too weak. That much is a fact of nature. Though... because you are mine, I would at least avenge you.
900260.lose: This pain... I shall return it tenfold!

201200.detail: Commander, I'm pretty proud of my trophies... Would you like to take a look?
201200.touch: This isn't a hunting rifle. It's a torpedo tube.
201200.login: Commander. How about we go hunting?
201200.hp_warning: The prey this time... is pretty tough...
201200.feeling2: Is there... a hunting ground around here?
201200.mission_complete: What? You want me to sound the horn of victory...?
201200.main: This guy over here? He's my treasured companion.|I don't dislike Hardy. It's just that she tends to be annoying when she's around.|These clothes...? Commander, you don't have to copy my dress when we go hunting.
201200.feeling5: When this war ends, I want to go hunting with you, Commander. ...Yes, just the two of us.
201200.upgrade: Hm, I guess I'll go for some bigger prey next time...
201200.unlock: Hello, Commander. I'm Hunter... Was there something else I was supposed to say...?
201200.feeling4: Commander, what would you like to eat tonight? I'll go catch some of whatever you want.
201200.propose: A hunter should always stalk his prey, but... having a base... no, a "home"... doesn't sound bad at all.
201200.skill: You'll only suffer more the more you struggle.
201200.profile: Royal Navy H-class destroyer, Hunter. I was taken down by Iron Blood destroyers in the battle of Narvik. It's nothing new for a hunter to end up being eaten by their prey...
201200.win_mvp: It's easy as long as I think of the enemy as my prey...
201200.expedition: You can never be too prepared.
couple_encourage: Hardy, lower your voice. You're too loud.
201200.mail: Here's your mail. Is there any information on what we should hunt next?
201200.feeling3: There is no prey a hunter cannot take down. Any failure should be attributed to a lack of sufficient preparation.
201200.lose: The hunter can become the hunted at any point...

105110.detail: Do not doubt my combat performance, Commander.
105110.touch: This should be... a friendly gesture I suppose.
105110.login: You’re late... the exercise has already begun, hurry!
105110.battle: The humiliation I once suffered... I'll repay you double!
105110.hp_warning: Getting hit by a torpedo... it feels bad.
105110.feeling2: I was once seriously injured, but then I was greatly enhanced during the process for my repairs…
105110.mission_complete: The mission was nicely executed, good one.
105110.main: The combat exercise didn’t go well… Is the Commander being lazy again? |I will never forget the humiliation I suffered on that day. |On the night of the Surigao Strait, I witnessed the last moments of the Sakura Empire fleet... They truly are a worthy opponent...
105110.feeling5: Commander, you have become someone who can completely take charge on the battlefield. At last, my powers have found a worthy partner... What? A love confession? Don't you trick me to say that, you fool——
105110.upgrade: It seems the Spokane Cup this year will still be mine.
105110.unlock: It’s finally my time to show my strength... Under the guidance of fate, the third ship of Colorado class, West Virginia, reporting in.
105110.feeling4: After joining your fleet, the answer to my question has been gradually answered... This power of mine is destined to protect everyone including you, Commander. My strength still has its value, even if I'm no longer the heroine of the battlefield.
105110.feeling1: Commander's laziness is almost beyond my bottom line.
105110.propose: You’ve decided to perform a pledge ritual with me? Commander really made a bold decision... In that case, I will not let your expectation down. I'll guard you until the very end.
105110.drop_descrip: Colorado class battleship— West Virginia, hull number BB-48.
105110.skill: Have a taste of my 406mm guns!
105110.profile: During a "Naval Holiday", my sisters and I were honored amongst the world's strongest battleships. We were granted the high-profile title of - BIG SEVEN. Although times are changing, the three of us still have the strength to fight any enemy fleet in a decisive battle, please don't forget that.
105110.touch2: Commander, it seems you’re rather close to getting lectured by me.
105110.mission: Carrying out missions is an important part of enhancing the strength of the fleet.
105110.home: What a peaceful port, it reminds me of Hawaii before the war.
105110.win_mvp: Have you seen this? This is the inevitably tragic ending of those who dare challenge the BIG SEVEN.
105110.expedition: The commission fleet is really efficient. I hope the Commander can learn a thing or two about efficiency.
105110.mail: Could these be letters from my sisters?
105110.feeling3: I’m proud of my BIG SEVEN title. But aircraft carriers seem to be replacing us battleships in naval battles. I am losing myself in all this confusion: this strength that I possess... what is it for?
105110.lose: I don't want to recall the humiliation I suffered on that day...!

900264.detail: Could you help me pick up that handkerchief...? I'd lose my balance if I try to pick it up myself...
900264.touch: It's as though... I've received your recognition, Commander. I feel so relieved.
900264.login: Greetings, Commander. I've tidied up a bit here. What do you think?
900264.feeling2: Commander, what do you find most important in a girl? Seriously, could you look me in the eyes when we're speaking?
900264.mission_complete: Don't forget to collect your rewards, Commander!
900264.main: Have you seen where did I put my planes? Oh? Right in front of me? Sorry, something blocked my line of sight.| Commander... can you feel my heartbeat through the palm of your hand?|Commander, why are you always staring at me? Am I that pretty?
900264.feeling5: No matter what you ask of me, Commander, I'll accept it... So, Commander, please tell me how you feel about me.
900264.upgrade: This way we can radiate our brilliance even further.
900264.unlock: Greetings, Commander! Aircraft carrier Illustrious reporting in! I pray that you will bring love and peace to this world. May the light be with you.
900264.feeling4: Commander... do you want to try... a soft landing?
900264.feeling1: Not even my light can reach the darkness within your heart?
900264.propose: Even though light should be shared equally among us all, it's fine for you to have a bit more. After all, I've received something important from the Commander as well.
900264.drop_descrip: Illustrious-class aircraft carrier – Illustrious, Hull Number 87!
900264.profile: Greetings, Commander. I am the armored aircraft carrier Illustrious. I may seem gentle, but I have quite the temper. I single-handedly bullied the Italian fleet during the raid at Taranto.
900264.touch2: Seriously, Commander, you're like a little kid.
900264.mission: Commander, it's no good to leave missions unfinished.
900264.home: Feeling tired? Relax for a while. How about a massage?
900264.win_mvp: The light shines upon our land of triumph.
900264.expedition: The light shall disperses the fog of darkness. Oh? The girls are back!
couple_encourage: How's Saratoga doing these days?
May the light illuminate Kaede's Legion!
900264.mail: Here's your mail, Commander! Should I open it for you?
900264.feeling3: Commander, while I'm like this, I take a special liking towards suprise night attacks. Seriously, I didn't mean it like that, but is the Commander into things like that?
900264.lose: Let's retreat, lest I lose my life...

802012.detail: Be they simple dresses or extravagant costumes, any outfit can be romantic once you actually put it on!
802012.touch: Hehe~ I will perform a little number called "The Maid's Dance" for you~
802012.login: "Welcome back, Master~" – Just like how all the Royal Maids do it~
802012.main: Wouldn't it be lovely if these stuffed toys could join me for a dance~?|I've heard people describe their dreams as astonishing or romantic. I wonder, have you had any fascinating dreams like that, Commander?|I'm more fond of imparting my passion to others through actions than through words while sitting down~
802012.unlock: I heard of this romantic concept of maid outfits, and thought I'd try one on to see how it feels~ What are your thoughts, Commander?
802012.drop_descrip: I heard of this romantic concept of maid outfits, and thought I'd try one on to see how it feels~ What are your thoughts, Commander?
802012.touch2: This sort of lust is not what romance is about!
802012.home: You know what comes next? Mhm! Tell me what's on your mind and your worries will all go away, Commander♪

306070.detail: I learned the power of submarines firsthand in that great war. While it's too late to turn back now, I can't help but wonder how I would be perceived if I hadn't been remodeled into an aircraft carrier.
306070.touch: Commander, are you able to fathom this majestic outfit that impeccably balances both beauty and dignity?
306070.login: You have kept me waiting... No, it's nothing. I can deal with this.
306070.battle: I've been pent up for a while. You'd better believe I'm going to give you a piece of my mind!
306070.hp_warning: Ugh, at a time like this...!
306070.feeling2: The sea of the Sakura Empire is nostalgic, but I also have murky and mixed feelings about it... No, that's got nothing to do with me right now. Focus, focus.
306070.mission_complete: We were able to handle the mission flawlessly thanks to your hard work, Commander.
306070.main: Looking after submarines is really rough... Th-This is from personal experience, so please believe me! | It's in my personality to not care what humans may think about me. This is the attitude that us warships ought to have as warriors.|From time to time, I become envious of the standard carriers... If only... I could be as strong as them...
306070.feeling5: Commander, because I have been by your side, I have been able to demonstrate my true ability. Thus, would it be okay to be my true self when I am beside you...? M-My true self usually leaks out quite often? I-Is that so?!
306070.upgrade: I'm truly grateful for your kindness, Commander.
306070.unlock: Remodeled Taigei-class Submarine Tender, Zuihou-class Light Carrier Ryuuhou, reporting for duty. I will strive to bring you victory, Commander! Yes, this time, I won't be held back by failures on my path to victory!
306070.feeling4: I take pride in the honor I have earned with my two hands. And that honor becomes fuel for further progress. ...Th-Thus, Commander, I implore you to send me out on sorties more often!
306070.feeling1: Commander, for some reason, you seem really unapproachable...
306070.propose: I, Ryuuhou, vow to be at your side, through thick and thin... W-Well then, from now on, I will not hide any part of myself from you, so prepare yourself... okay?
306070.profile: While I was able to set sail many times during my time both as a submarine tender and as a light carrier, in the end, I was unable to take even a single step away from port... No, nothing will happen if I just sit around like this. As I have stated many times, I, Ryuuhou, will bring you victory!
306070.mission: A new mission... If it's a directive from the top brass, let's take care of it right away.
306070.home: Good work, Commander. Let's take a short break. ...But you shouldn't rest for too long, because we're going to review some battles right after this!
306070.win_mvp: Unperturbed by both victory and defeat. This is my pride as a member of the Sakura Empire... hehe!
306070.expedition: The commissions have been completed. I shall go ahead and greet them first. ...I hope their bounty is plentiful.
couple_encourage: Let us go together!
You're from that time...
Houshou! Let's do our best together!
Ahhhh, please don't hug me right now!
306070.mail: A letter has arrived. I'm curious about its contents... Are you not?
306070.feeling3: Commander, are you interested in things like commendations or admonishments? ...N-No, it's nothing. I was just curious...
306070.lose: I-I shall let you win just this once!

101150.detail: Ah! D-don't touch me anywhere weird, okay...
101150.touch: I'm sorry that I don't live up to your expectations, Commander...
101150.login: C-Commander... N-no, I wasn't waiting that long!
101150.battle: Commander... I'll work hard not to disappoint you!
101150.main: Commander, it's so warm here! I think I can relax like this...|Thatcher's over there! She's making me anxious~!|Ausburne isn't like Thatcher at all... She actually helps me when I need it!
101150.feeling5: C-C-Commander... I just watched a film in which two people really liked each other... but they couldn't be together in the end... We'll be together forever, right?
101150.upgrade: U-u-umm... I'll try to work harder now!
101150.unlock: Huh...? C-C-C-Commander... Hello... Spence h-has been wanting to talk to you... b-but didn't have the courage to...
101150.feeling4: C-C-Commander, can I come stay with you when it's storming outside? I'm terrified of thunder!
101150.propose: So you like me too, Commander? W-w-w-what will I do now... I'm so happy that I can't stop crying...!
101150.drop_descrip: Fletcher-class destroyer - Spence, Hull Number DD-512!
101150.profile: I'm... Spence from the Little Beavers. I took part in the Great Marianas Turkey Shoot with my younger sisters. Oh no! A h-h-hurricane is coming... Sorry, Commander, I forget everything when I get nervous!
101150.touch2: Eeek~! Um... W-what am I supposed to...
101150.mission: Commander... You haven't finished all of your missions...
101150.home: You're back in one piece, Commander... Thank the lord!
101150.expedition: The girls are back! I'm so jealous of how awesome they all are!
101150.feeling3: My big sister said... that I can trust you, Commander...

408110.detail: I think it's good for a submarine to act a bit more mysterious. Wouldn't you agree, Commander?
408110.touch: Just give me the signal when you wanna slack off. Hehehe~
408110.login: Oh, you're back. Ready to start chipping away at this mountain of paperwork?
408110.battle: There's nothing to worry about. Just take it easy.
408110.feeling2: A submarine must be slippery, elusive. You know, an unknown threat lurking beneath the surface. Hehehe...
408110.mission_complete: Accomplishing a mission can be the reward in and of itself. Receiving tangible things is a nice bonus, though.
408110.main: Sauerkraut juice is a great pick-me-up. Give it a try and see for yourself.|Penelope? Oh right, she works here too. Take good care of her, you hear?|You can't figure out what that report says? Let me see... What, I'm too close to you? Hmm... Well, my bad~
408110.feeling5: Why don't we start dating, Commander? ...What's this out of the blue? I've taken my sweet time preparing, and this is the time to strike! Hehehe, now give yourself to me~♡
408110.upgrade: Bolstering your combat abilities is always a good move.
408110.unlock: Formally, I'm the Type VIIC submarine U-410. But you, Commander, can call me whatever resonates with your heart. You heard that right: just let your heart decide. Hehehe~
408110.feeling4: I've got someone on the hook. What do I mean by that? You'll have to wait to find out. That's part of what being patient is about.
408110.feeling1: I just don't know what to do with inconsiderate jerks like you.
408110.propose: Ooh, I see you've been preparing something of your own. So, have you made your mind? You'll live the rest of your days happily with me? ...Great, then we're all set♪
408110.drop_descrip: Iron Blood Type VIIC submarine – U-410.
408110.profile: For an Iron Blood "wolf," I don't have much to boast about. I went on a few patrols and the odd rescue mission, but that's about it... I just wish my career would've ended out at sea instead of docked at port.
408110.touch2: Are you saying you find my body "too good to pass up?"
408110.mission: Do you find it thrilling to put off your missions until the last minute?
408110.home: Haste makes waste. Take it easy, yeah?
408110.win_mvp: You'll need to do better than that, my surface ship friends.
408110.expedition: The commission team has come back in one piece. That's nice to see.
couple_encourage: There's no escaping the wolfpack!
Yeah, that's it! Draw the enemy closer!
408110.mail: Letting your mail pile up just to read through it all at once might feel rewarding, but it's not very productive.
408110.feeling3: Patience is the most valuable trait a submarine can have. What lengths would you go, how long would you wait for someone dear to you, Commander? Hehehe~
408110.lose: There's no turning this battle around... We should probably retreat.

802011.detail: Commander, how about a game of beach volleyball? I actually happen to be quite good at it♪
802011.touch: Go on ahead without you? Why, a secretary can't just casually part from her Commander, can she? I'll be right here waiting for you♪
802011.login: Commander, don't forget to stretch before going into the ocean, okay?
802011.main: Commander, could I ask you to apply sunscreen to my skin next time we go to the beach?|Long hair is quite inconvenient when you're swimming... Which way of tying up my hair is your favorite, Commander?|Oh, Commander~ Since we're going to the beach, why not change into your swim gear ahead of time? Oh, no, I definitely don't want to see how it looks on you, not at all~
802011.unlock: Commander, does my swimsuit pique your fancy? I'm actually quite proud of my fashion sense. *Giggle* Now, let's enjoy midsummer together~
802011.drop_descrip: Commander, does my swimsuit pique your fancy? I'm actually quite proud of my fashion sense. *Giggle* Now, let's enjoy midsummer together~
802011.touch2: It seems as summer comes forth, so too does your passion~
802011.home: My, you're so excited, Commander♪ I knew you were looking forward to the beach~

301259.detail: Yuugure has come a long way. She's no longer the little girl constantly tugging at my sleeves asking for help.
301259.touch: Jeez, Commander, why are you tugging on my sleeve like Yuugure now?
301259.login: You seem pretty busy today too. But don't worry, I'll help you out~
301259.main: Yuugure's all grown up now. When I stand next to her, you can't even tell who's the older sister anymore! Ehehe...|Wish I got as big an upgrade to my ability to take care of people as I did to my firepower. It's not just Yuugure, it's practically the entire 27th Destroyer Division... I just can't keep up with all of them.|Here Commander, your lunchbox. I made a portion for Yuugure as well.
301259.unlock: Ah... So this is what it feels like to be retrofitted. I'll work harder for your sake, and for everyone in the 27th Destroyer Division~
301259.drop_descrip: Ah... So this is what it feels like to be retrofitted. I'll work harder for your sake, and for everyone in the 27th Destroyer Division~

207033.drop_descrip: This is my first time wearing such exotic fashion, hehe~. Commander, if you like how I look, how about showing me off a little~?

308051.detail: The other kids often post all kinds of pictures onto social media from their phones... Commander, you can also take a look.
308051.touch: ... What's the matter, Commander? Oh, I was just watching that couple over there walking to school together...
308051.battle: I hope this doesn't get in the way of my school attendance...
308051.main: At school, you can see a completely different side of people. It can be pretty interesting... |I've received invitations from several clubs before... but I still prefer to watch others from a distance. |Don't worry, Commander. I'm enjoying my time at school.
308051.unlock: School... is pretty nice. I can quietly stay in this corner and mind my own business...
308051.drop_descrip: School... is pretty nice. I can quietly stay in this corner and mind my own business...
308051.mission: New text message...? Um, Commander, new missions have been posted.
308051.home: Commander, I just got out of school... Um, want to head back together?

307020.detail: Commander, if you keep looking at me like that, you’ll be eaten up.
307020.login: Justice and righteousness are for the strong only. The weak can only weep in vain.
307020.battle: Entertain me with your final struggles. Hehehe...
307020.hp_warning: It’s time for a death match! Heheh- hehehe!
307020.feeling2: The weak will be eliminated. If you cannot accept that, then simply become stronger.
307020.mission_complete: Here are the rewards, the fruits of your labor.
307020.main: I shall conquer all, no matter who stands against me.|Our enemies may be strong, but that is what makes them worth crushing. Heheh...|The girls of the Fifth Carrier Division? They might amount to something if they work hard enough.
307020.feeling5: I have so much I want to say, but I forget them all the moment I see your face...
307020.upgrade: Not bad. I’ve come up with some new combat techniques.
307020.unlock: Will I be able to find a worthy foe here? Very well. I’m yours. Perhaps this, too, is destiny.
307020.feeling4: I cannot comprehend these emotions... is this some sort of primal instinct?
307020.feeling1: It seems like you're not the hero I was looking for...
307020.propose: ... Is this for me? Hm... perhaps it is fate for the strong to be drawn to each other. If that is the case, I shall follow my instincts then. Hehehe~
307020.skill: Only the strong may survive on the battlefield!
307020.profile: I am {namecode:92}, from the First Carrier Division. I was originally designed to be a battleship, but fate had different plans or me. Enemies? I simply slaughter them, but only because it is my duty, not for fun.
307020.touch2: ... Fine. If you say it helps you relax...
307020.mission: Commander, stop slacking around. There are still missions to complete.
307020.home: A fitting reward for the ears of our enemies. Let us enjoy the spoils of war leisurely.
307020.win_mvp: Such is the fate of the weak. Death, nothing more.
307020.expedition: The girls on commission have returned. Go on ahead, I will prepare some refreshments for them.
couple_encourage: Sister, please take this seriously.
The First Carrier Division is not to be looked down upon!
I did not expect to be fighting alongside you all...
307020.mail: Your mail is here. Try not to forget it next time.
307020.feeling3: Should you be defeated one day, it simply means that you were too weak. That much is a fact of nature. Though... because you are mine, I would at least avenge you.
307020.lose: This pain... I shall return it tenfold!

900278.detail: Everyone's faces are full of laughter here... I think I am rather fond of this place!
900278.login: Welcome ba... oww, I bit my tongue...
900278.hp_warning: The decisive battle is upon us!
900278.feeling2: What do you require of me? Hmm? I am not doing anything in particular. After I handed the work to Yamato, there is little to do except fight.
900278.mission_complete: The mission rewards... Ngh...! Phew... is it acceptable to leave them here?
900278.feeling5: It is enough to be treasured by one person? Since you were the one who brought me out... I shall have you take responsibility... that is, umm, in other words, I command you to... treasure me... if that is acceptable?
900278.upgrade: I hope... to be able to welcome the day when we can all beat our swords into plowshares...
900278.unlock: I am called Nagato, flagship of the Sakura Empire's Combined Fleet. Are you the one known as the Commander? I shall bear witness to whether or not you have the ability to unite this world.
900278.feeling4: I see! I am less intimidating with my riggings taken off. I certainly do feel lighter... but why does it feel like I've lost something... like when I appointed Yamato to take over as flagship?
900278.profile: I am the manifestation of the soul of the Sakura Empire, the pride and glory of her warrior spirit. As a Big Seven, I am also the symbol of an era. Open your eyes and bask in my radiance... You may stop basking now, I'm getting a bit sleepy...
900278.feeling1: Your wish... is to repeat the errors of the past once more? Very well... I see...
900278.propose: When I cross the river after the war ends, what awaits me is not a searing white light that engulfs everything, but rather, your warm embrace... There is nothing more that I could ask for...
900278.skill: I am called Nagato... Nagato of the Sakura Empire!
900278.touch: ...! N-No one has ever dared to lay hands on me in such a manner...
900278.mission: Is it acceptable to arrange the itinerary in this manner? I do not quite understand how to do it yet...
900278.home: I have never had to welcome anyone before. Perhaps I shall do so by firing my cannons?
900278.win_mvp: Impudent fools... why did they have to provoke me?
900278.expedition: The commission fleet has returned... H-Hey, I managed to remember the time. Have you no words of praise for me?
900278.mail: What is this piece of paper? "Mail?" I see, it's mail. Shall I read it?
900278.feeling3: I should spend more time with the others? Even if I tried to do that, I would not know how to behave, and they would be afraid of me all the same... Hey, what are you doing... why are you taking off my riggings?!
900278.lose: Ugh... I have failed once again...

107092.detail: By the way, Commander, there's nobody else around, right? *sigh*... Thank god... If Enterprise or Shangri-La saw me like this, I'd die of— ...Eh?! Shangri-La?! Wait, no, stop! Please, no photossssss!!
107092.touch: One more cup... Just one more! Commander, here! Cheers! Thanks for everything you're always doing for us. This is... a token of gratitude from me... *hic*!
107092.login: Sorry, Commander, but could you give me a hand? ...Ugh, why is the hem of this dress so long...
107092.mission_complete: Did the mission rewards already get here? Th-thank god...
107092.main: I even got Mr. Eagle here all decked out~ Looks pretty sharp and spiffy, right?|Hey... Commander, um... Yeah, so... have you ever seen Enterprise get drunk before? Ah, no, I was just asking out of curiosity... I mean, it's almost impossible to picture that happening to her, right?|Commander, don't worry about me. Don't you think you should head back to the venue before the others start to wonder where you went?
107092.feeling5: The princess and the prince snuggled up to one another and sailed into the sea of stars above the castle~ ...Did you hear that?! Ah, forget it... Just write it off as me being drunk... and let me cling to you already! Hehe, ehehehe...
107092.unlock: Commander?! Ah, um, no, I'm not drunk! ...I, uh, just had a bit too much to drink... just a bit! Please don't tell the others though!
107092.drop_descrip: Commander?! Ah, um, no, I'm not drunk! ...I, uh, just had a bit too much to drink... just a bit! Please don't tell the others though!
107092.touch2: Commander! Jeez, what are you doing... Did you also have a bit too much to drink? What am I going to do...
107092.mission: We've got new work? Um, I really hope my head clears up soon... Ugh, everything's still spinning...
107092.home: Everyone was greeting me one after another at the party, and there I was basking in their attention, so... I started toasting everyone, and... Ugh! Why am I so childish...?!
107092.expedition: Wh-why is a commission fleet coming back now of all times? ...Commander, I'll— *hic*...! I don't think I should go like this after all...

301100.detail: Everyone in the 6th DesDiv is super unique! There's Ikazuchi, Inazuma, and we even have Akatsuki the ninja! I love everyone! Ehehe~
301100.touch: Yo! Did you call me, Commander?
301100.login: Commander, did you just pop in~? All righty... Let's both get some good work done today!
301100.battle: Heheh~ Hibiki is super strong~! If you don't believe me, just take a look at this~♪
301100.hp_warning: I won't let it end like this!
301100.feeling2: I've been making Akatsuki worried all this time. I have to apologize to her properly, as well as thank her.
301100.mission_complete: Missionnnn... complete! ...Hey, Commander, you should get pumped up too!
301100.main: Verniy...? It has a nostalgic ring to it... |I'm so glad that we can all be together again~♪ |If you don't need me for anything, I'm going to go play with Ikazuchi and Inazuma~
301100.feeling5: Commander, why don't you tell me your story? I'm really interested! ...Why? No particular reason~ Haven't we exhausted all the other topics already? Ehehe~
301100.upgrade: So this is that "leveling up" thing that Ikazuchi mentioned? Nihihi~
301100.unlock: Nihihi~ We finally meet at last, Commander! The name's Hibiki! Don't you forget it!
301100.feeling4: Ah, that reminds me! Commander, have you been taking care of yourself properly? We'd be in serious trouble if you got sick and collapsed or something... Well, even if that happened to you, Hibiki would tenderly nurse you back to health~♪
301100.feeling1: Commander, it seems like the only way to get you to open your eyes is to get a bit rough... *sigh*...
301100.propose: I've been waiting so long for this! Ehehe~ I love you, Commander! ...Ah, look at you getting all bashful~ But my turn's not over yet. I love love love you~! Ehehe~
301100.drop_descrip: Type III Akatsuki-class destroyer number two – Hibiki.
301100.profile: I'm Hibiki, from the 6th DesDiv~♪ I fought in many battles with my friends, and even saw the end of things. That's good and all, but... having to go in for repairs at that time was a bit awkward... Ahaha...
301100.touch2: Ah~! Commander, I bet you did that on purpose just now!
301100.mission: We sure have all sorts of different missions, huh... Don't sweat it though! I'll help you out!
301100.home: Good work out there~ Well, having that said, you still have a lot of stuff that needs to be done... Ahaha...
301100.win_mvp: Heheh~ I'll be taking that gold star~!
301100.expedition: Ah, that's right, the commission fleet seems to have returned? Should I go with you to welcome them back?
couple_encourage: Woah, are you a phoenix as well?
6th DesDiv, set sail!
Maybe you're a real phoenix!
Akatsuki, let's do this, together!
Ikazuchi, be careful for unseen enemies!
Inazuma, be on the lookout for unseen enemies!
301100.mail: Mail? Show me as well! Show me!
301100.feeling3: Akatsuki, you've been pretty gung-ho about getting the 6th DesDiv back together... Well, the name's not that important as long as we're all together. That's what I think anyway~
301100.lose: Awww... Looks like I'll have to go back to port for repairs...

802013.drop_descrip: Modest though it may be, isn't this a lovely little garden? Come, Commander! Let us dance surrounded by Mother Nature~

10100010.detail: It's so embarrassing when people stare at me like that.
10100010.touch: Ahahah! That tickles! Stop it, will you!
10100010.login: Welcome back! Let's give it all we've got, nep!
10100010.battle: Witness the might of a protagonist!
10100010.hp_warning: Nep?! It's not time to panic just yet!
10100010.feeling2: Going out for some exercise every now and then isn't so bad! Hey, Commander! What do you say we go for a walk together next time?
10100010.main: Heheh! How's my rigging look? It's all so Azur Laney! Looks good on me, don'tcha think?|Nep nep♪ Nep nep♪ Nep nep neppynep♪|I'm hungry... Go get me some pudding, Commander!
10100010.feeling5: What should we play today? How about "who's-their-crush"? Hmm, your crush... that's gotta be me! Heheh, spot on, aren't I?
10100010.unlock: Heya! My name's Neptune! Nice to meet you!
10100010.feeling4: Commander obtained! Now we're gonna play some games together! Listen: you're not getting any sleep tonight.
10100010.feeling1: Huh? What was that? I can't hear you, I've got bananas stuck in my ears.
10100010.propose: Tell you the truth, I was nervous when I first came to this world, but now after meeting you and becoming your special someone... I'm happy from the bottom of my heart that I came here. So, here's hoping for a bright future together!
10100010.drop_descrip: Heya! My name's Neptune! Nice to meet you!
10100010.profile: I'm the protiest of protagonists, Neptune! I'm the CPU of a country called Planeptune. What's a CPU? It's a long story, so I'll tell you another time.
10100010.touch2: Hey! You can't do that, Commander!
10100010.mission: Me, do some missions? I'll help if you give me 5 servings of pudding, how's that? ...I'm just kidding! Let's get out there and finish it!
10100010.home: Oh, the pudding is calling out to me...! We gotta get back home!
10100010.win_mvp: Justice will always win! Just kidding...
10100010.expedition: Hey! Everyone's back! Shouldn't we head out and welcome them?
couple_encourage: Hey, Noire! Let's see who can beat the most enemies!
All right! Let's go, everyone!
10100010.mail: You have new mail! Now's not the time for pudding!
10100010.feeling3: I've got an idea! Commander, you should visit Planeptune sometime! I'm sure everyone would love to meet you!
10100010.lose: We regret to inform you that Neppy has been defeated.

308050.detail: Eep?! Oh, C-Commander... did you need something?
308050.touch: Commander, what's the matter? Ah, umm... was I muttering something weird to myself again?!
308050.login: Eep?! C-Commander... it's fine to not greet me...
308050.hp_warning: L-Looks like I've drawn too much attention...
308050.feeling2: If you don't want to get caught up in bothersome things, it's probably better to be like thin air and not stand out...
308050.mission_complete: *gasp*! Oh no... I spaced out while tallying the mission rewards...
308050.main: Commander, you're always dealing with so many people every day... Amazing... I-I'd never be able to do that... |Commander, being together with you is peaceful and quiet... I can calm down and think about lots of things... |Being athletic like 58 and 19.... err, I mean, 26... would be nice... Eek?! C-Commander? I-I didn't say anything!!
308050.feeling5: Commander, sorry I haven't come to see you recently... It's just that... I've been thinking about you like crazy, and I can't stop it... It's so embarrassing...
308050.unlock: I've been found... I... I'm I-56... Um, if there are any missions I can do by myself, could I get those?
308050.feeling4: From time to time, my thoughts slip out when I'm muttering to myself... D-don't read too much into it...
308050.propose: Am... am I still fantasizing? Mmhm... probably, yup... Commander, give my cheeks a good pinch...!
308050.drop_descrip: Type B3 Mod. 2 cruiser submarine – I-56.
308050.profile: I am the 2nd ship of the Type-B Mod. 2 cruiser submarines, I-56. The most noteworthy thing about me... is that I did nothing noteworthy... But there wasn't much I could do at that point anyway...
308050.touch2: Eek?! C-Commander... this is just like in that book...?! Ah, um, forget I said that! Sorry...
308050.mission: Commander, these... these are mission delegations, right...?
308050.win_mvp: Next time... I hope I don't get MVP...
308050.expedition: What's the commission of the composition team... Umm, I mean, the composition of the...
couple_encourage: Who would I work best with...
308050.mail: Make sure to go through your mail carefully...
308050.feeling3: Everyone in the fleet gets along so well... Ehe... hehehe... Um, it's nothing... l-leave me alone...

102160.detail: If you intend to keep me by your side, you'd better carefully observe my every move!
102160.touch: Hm? You'd like to see me while I'm training? Very well... you'd better burn this into your eyes!
102160.login: Commander, you sure took your time getting here. Come on, let's set sail. Can you keep up with me?
102160.battle: Let's go! I want to see everyone at their best!
102160.hp_warning: We can't afford to be careless!
102160.feeling2: Next, I'll handle the paperwork and review the training plans. Commander, make sure to check my work properly. Don't slow me down, got it?
102160.mission_complete: You've earned these rewards. Take a look when you have time.
102160.main: Capturing everyone's attention with my brilliant performance at Naval Reviews - that's the way I like to do things. |Because of my hectic schedule, I never got much time to relax back in port... But that's fine, someone like me ought to be busy, wouldn't you agree~? |You want me to bring you back a souvenir next time? Should you really be asking that while you still have work to do?
102160.feeling5: You feel uneasy when I'm not around? Don't worry, I'll always be here to escort you. As a matter of fact, you should make sure to always be around me.
102160.upgrade: I wonder if I'll be even better at my escort duties now?
102160.unlock: Hmm, so you're the commander here? Don't worry, I'll carry out my duties as an escort ship. But first, you'll have to meet my standards!
102160.feeling4: Sidling up to me this closely... Are you trying to smell my hair? Hehe, how is it? Does it remind you of the sea breeze?
102160.feeling1: Hmph. If it's about me ignoring you, you brought this upon yourself!
102160.propose: Do you feel honored? You've managed to earn my recognition. From here on out, I'll have high expectations for you, so don't let me down~

10100080.upgrade: My beauty has been sculpted even more.

10100080.feeling4: I have some free time tonight, so I would be glad to help you with work. Afterwards, I'd like you to give me... U-um... forget I said anything.
10100080.feeling1: I have nothing to say to you.

10100080.drop_descrip: I am the CPU of Leanbox, Green Heart. No matter who the enemy is, I will not hold back. Are you ready?

Alright, let's go！

301101.headtouch: Want to know more about oni horn? Or this golden badge here?

900311.detail: Staring at me all day won't turn you into an expert!
900311.login: Righty tighty, Lefty loosey, Stay calm and Purin on!
900311.battle: Purin~! Don't stop until they kneel and cry!
900311.feeling2: My sister is so dumb. When people talk about our colors, it's not about our hair, it's about ra... rari... ah, now I remember! Reality TV!

900311.feeling5: You're not an average commander if you managed to conquer my heart. But I won't be shy or blush! Instead I'll give you a growl! Graaaah!

900311.feeling4: Whee~! I'm flying! So~ high! Hey, don't move! You'll have to catch me if I fall!
900311.feeling1: You're pretty amazing to have gotten on my bad side! But I won't get angry just to appease you! Haha! Enjoy your emptiness!
900311.propose: As a simple Bulin, I'm meant to just help strengthen your other ships... But you gave me this ring... You're a strange one! I like you! Come, let's raise our hands together and say purin~ purin~!
900311.drop_descrip: Prototype Bulin MKII. Can be used to limit break all Super Rare ships.
900311.skill: My drill is the drill that will pierce the heavens!
900311.profile: Hahaha! It's your lucky day now that you've met me! We can purin together from this day forward! What for? To make everyone stronger, obviously! How do you purin? Like this! Purin~! Purin~!
900311.touch2: Purin~ purin~! (Prototype Bulin MKII continues to spin faster)
900311.mission: Purin~! The next mission has been chosen for you!
900311.home: Let's run around and relax! Purin~!
900311.expedition: Yaaaay~! Commander! The girls who went out on a commission have come back! Let's drill something to celebrate!
900311.feeling3: I'll let you in on a little secret. My little sister keeps telling people that she's smarter than me. But truth is, she's dumber! I try to be nice and let her feel good about herself, like a big sister should. Ha!
900311.lose: So why am I on the battlefield anyway, purin?!

203079.detail: If the Force means something, it means having the will to always fight! And I will fight until I've overcome my destiny!
203079.touch: Now, grasp my hand firmly! ... Could you feel my enhanced Force?
203079.login: For us to meet in this place, at this hour... There is no mistaking it; this is fate!

203079.touch2: W-wait! Continue, and my Force will swallow you whole– Eek!

900310.win_mvp: Bulin! I've successfully buli buli'd the enemies!
900310.lose: Ehh? I thought I was supposed to be stronger, bulin?

Commander, you should come and have a dip too!

101430.mail: Don't you forget, I'm the one who brought you the mail!
101430.feeling3: It might be hard to stand out from the rest of the Fletchers, but... Commander, I know you'll be able to come up with something!

408082.login: Are you waiting on U-110 too, Commander?

408082.drop_descrip: I have to wear beautiful clothes to a party, or so Bulldog said. So, I had everyone help me pick out beautiful clothes. Commander, I'm beautiful, right? Eh... cute?

102162.detail: Commander, are you here to trick-or-treat? Here, I got this candy from Abercrombie.
