102162.drop_descrip: We have to work hard if we want to play hard, isn't that right, Commander? Are you ready for our happy Halloween?
102162.touch2: ... I should just boot you off the broomstick and be done with it!
102162.home: Everyone has a different way of enjoying Halloween. Hehe, that's how it should be~

10600031.detail: Um, Commander... Could you please not stare at me... because... it's a bit embarrassing...
10600031.touch: We're taking photos? Well, I'm a bit camera shy, but... okay. How's this pose? Should I stay like this?
10600031.login: Are you here for some relaxation as well, Commander? Have yourself a nice, prolonged break from all that paperwork you're used to.
10600031.main: What's your favorite drink, Commander? I'm partial to the... iced café au lait, I suppose.|Commander, are you good at swimming? I'm just curious to see how fast your breaststroke is!|There's nothing... off about my swimsuit, is there?
10600031.unlock: I was amazed to see the port had such a scenic place as this... Truly, you can't go without taking this view in. Right, Commander?
10600031.drop_descrip: I was amazed to see the port had such a scenic place as this... Truly, you can't go without taking this view in. Right, Commander?
10600031.home: You would think shipgirls are excellent swimmers, since they do so much battle at sea... But perhaps that isn't necessarily the case?

900275.detail: Look, isn't Elizabeth acting a bit too spoiled? And Warspite and the others are totally enabling that. I knew I should have been the one in charge... Huhh? I'm more or less the same...? Wh-what did you say?!
900275.touch: Speak your mind, my attendant. You have my ear.
900275.login: It's about time! Now, show me today's itinerary!
900275.hp_warning: H-hey, hurry up and do something about this...!
900275.feeling2: Good, you came. If you have no other work to do, play me in a game of chess.
900275.mission_complete: Even the most trivial quests at least deserve some rewards.
900275.upgrade: Not bad, my attendant~ Do you want a reward?
900275.unlock: To be Valiant is to be me. Remember this face, for it is the face of a fleet leader! ...Speaking of faces, who are you? The Commander? Very well! I shall treat you as my personal servant!
900275.feeling4: H-hold up! Chess is like a real-world exercise, so you have to consider all the various external factors! Th-that's right! That last match was a fake! A fluke! Doesn't count! Cancelled! Got it?!
900275.feeling1: I had great expectations for you...
900275.propose: Well done! You've gained my recognition as my trustiest spear in the arsenal! To reward you for your continued loyalty, I shall allow you to stay at my side and bask in my charisma! May this ring be a symbol of our bond~?
900275.skill: Everything dances within the palm of my hand!
900275.profile: Queen Elizabeth-class battleship, Valiant. Hehe, this fleet is known from Jutland to the Far East for its heroic majesty, and I am the reason for that! Now, Commander, you shall become my assistant so that you may prove your worth as a subordinate.
900275.touch2: What's the meaning of this?! Grrr... As a charismatic, generous, and VERY patient person, I will forgive you just this once!
900275.mission: I'll leave this these trifling quests to you.
900275.home: My attendant, how fares the combat situation? Do tell me in detail.

900275.expedition: Heheh, it seems that the commission team has been doing well. Do send them my best regards in my stead.
couple_encourage: Feast your eyes upon the might of the noble Queen Elizabeth-class!
M-make sure you observe my every move!
900275.mail: Tsk... Why is all the mail for you...
900275.feeling3: Y-you're better than I expected... F-fine, I won't go easy on you next time...!

10600051.drop_descrip: Whew! The wind feels great! ...What are you staring at me like that for, you silly dog? You're the one who said you wanted to go to the beach, remember? To start with, how about... we take a stroll?

802020.detail: Jeanne d'Arc... While this name imparts a heavy responsibility, I refuse to run away from it. After all, bearing that burden is my duty.
802020.login: May the port be ever blessed with our Lord's grace.
802020.hp_warning: The situation is dire... Everyone, stay in formation!
802020.feeling2: If thorns block my path, I will clear a way. If flames obstruct my path, I will overcome them. I will not let any obstacle keep me from walking the path of God!
802020.mission_complete: There is more value to mission than just the rewards.
802020.main: Saint Michael, I beseech you – please tell me what I should do next...|My name, my weapons, and my rigging. All are testament to my conviction.|If you're tired, you should rest. Battles should not compose your entire existence.
802020.feeling5: Commander... The more burdens I bear, the more I cannot allow myself to rest. That's why, for a little bit... just for a little bit... would you lend me your shoulder?
802020.upgrade: My burning spirit, become my strength!
802020.unlock: If you are familiar with the name I have been entrusted with, then you should also understand my noble calling. Jeanne d'Arc of Iris Libre is now under your command.
802020.feeling4: My dream is to lead everyone to victory while bearing a banner. However, victory is something that cannot be achieved alone. For that purpose, I need the help of my allies, and you, Commander.
802020.feeling1: ...If you are a demon, I will not hesitate to cut you down with my sword... If if is just that you have strayed from the righteous path, then repent, now!
802020.propose: This is... how you feel...? I'm so happy. I also treasure you the most, Commander. Um, you see... I'm not really sure what we're supposed to do together, but... first, would you like to try being pampered by me, Commander?
802020.skill: The Lord's blessings upon the Iris Libre!
802020.profile: Even though I had previously been a training cruiser in charge of raising excellent warriors, I am now standing at the front lines for my country with sword in hand. I pledge my all for my beloved homeland!
802020.touch2: I-is this what you're into, Commander?
802020.mission: Commander, there must still be some unfinished business you need to attend to.
802020.home: The flames of war have yet to be extinguished. It's time to redouble our efforts.
802020.win_mvp: This still isn't enough to fulfill our duty... No. Everyone, you've all done great!
802020.expedition: Everyone's returned safely. Praise be to the Lord!
couple_encourage: My comrade, may you also receive our Lord's blessings!
802020.mail: Commander, you've received some mail. Please look through it.
802020.feeling3: This blade does not exist to be wielded for my sake. I wield this blade for you, my homeland of Iris Libre, and for all in the fleet...

10600041.detail: Commander, did you ask my sister to participate in some photoshoots too? Hehe~ She might act all mean on the outside, but she'll do whatever you need as long as you don't ask for something risqué~
10600041.login: We're doing another shoot today? I don't mind, but...
10600041.main: After the shoot, wanna go grab some bubble milk tea? All right, no backsies!|Commander, are you taking some photos of the other girls as well? Let me have a look~|Commander, if you could go on a trip, where would you go?
10600041.unlock: A photoshoot? That'd be similar to what I did before coming here, but... um, this swimsuit is a bit much... Commander, is this what you're into? Geez... It's so embarrassing...
10600041.drop_descrip: A photoshoot? That'd be similar to what I did before coming here, but... um, this swimsuit is a bit much... Commander, is this what you're into? Geez... It's so embarrassing...
10600041.touch2: N-no, you can't! It's too embarrassing...
10600041.home: Yaaawn~ ...Oh, did I fall asleep? Sorry, the sofa was just too comfy...

900274.detail: To your friends, show no cowardice; to your foes, show no mercy – that is my creed. Hehehe~
900274.touch: Do save the massage for later. I'm not tired yet.
900274.login: How nice to see you. Now, let's get to work on today's tasks.
900274.battle: Heheh, there'll be no mercy for you!
900274.feeling2: "Shape the world into God's vision" – if there is a God, what is his ideal world? It can't be one of perpetual war, that's for sure.
900274.mission_complete: A mission's done. I can take care of claiming the rewards, no problem.
900274.feeling5: Bah, being indirect is just not like me. I adore you, Commander. Both as the leader of the fleet, and as my beloved special someone. I wish to know... do you adore me as well?
900274.upgrade: Phew... I'll return your gesture with valour on the battlefield, Commander.
900274.unlock: It's a pleasure meeting you, Commander. I'm Howe of the King George V-class. I hope we can build a healthy relationship.
900274.feeling4: Come visit the dorm next time we're having cookies, Commander. We'd all love to have you, and I especially want to spend some quality time with you.
900274.feeling1: A kind deed to others is a kind deed to yourself – or so I was naive enough to believe...
900274.propose: Thank you for your sincerity, Commander. I will gladly be yours. I won't ask of you to share all your joys and sorrows with me, as I'm more than happy with just being by your side. Ah, that didn't sound like what I would say, did it? Well, hehehe~
900274.drop_descrip: King George V-class battleship – Howe (HMS Howe.)
900274.profile: Prior to my being sent to the Pacific, I always worked side by side with George. But aside from the one time we escorted our Sardegnian friends, I suppose I don't have too many notable feats to my name.
900274.mission: Oh, missions? Are there any I can help with?
900274.home: Nicely done out there. If you've got the energy to spare, perhaps you could write an after-battle report?
900274.win_mvp: Heheh, I'm in top shape today!
900274.expedition: Do you need someone to escort the commission team home? I'm quite the experienced escort, I'll have you know.
couple_encourage: Allow me to witness your true might.
Let us show the world what we're made of.
Cookies are great, don't you know? Do you really not want one?
900274.mail: We've received what looks to be mail addressed to you.
900274.feeling3: Are you tired, Commander? Under the weather, perhaps? Heh, well, a nice cookie can fix that. Just eat one of these and you'll be right back to normal.
900274.lose: Next time... victory will be ours.

10600071.detail: "You want my fortune, do ya? Beat me in cards, and it's all yours, kid!" ...That's how they do those huge gambles in movies, right? Heheh!
10600071.touch: You've run out of chips? Now, that just won't do! Here you are. Spend them wisely, okay?
10600071.login: Welcome, Commander! Enjoy your stay at the Fantabulous Casino! Here are your chips for the day.
10600071.main: Would you like a nice, cold beverage? It'll clear your head, I can promise you that!|Be it at work or at the tables, you always need a clear head and a poker face! Those so happen to be my special skills!|Don't you think it's interesting how, even though the odds are the same for everyone, if there are winners, there must be losers too?|I see you blushing there, Commander. Heheh, eyes on the prize!
10600071.unlock: "Welcome to Monica's Fantabulous Casino! Where you can have your every whim satisfied!" ...Oh, that doesn't sound very casino-managery? Heheh!
10600071.drop_descrip: "Welcome to Monica's Fantabulous Casino! Where you can have your every whim satisfied!" ...Oh, that doesn't sound very casino-managery? Heheh!
10600071.touch2: A slave to temptation, are we? Heheh, you'll have to fix that if you want any favors from Lady Luck!
10600071.home: Are you having a good time, Commander? At the Fantabulous Casino, chips come free of charge! If you ever run out, do come see me!

802019.detail: As I am now, I'll surely be able to dance for you even more wonderfully!
802019.touch: The essence of dancing is to follow your own feelings. Come on, Commander! Allons danser!
802019.login: It's a wonderful day today as well, Commander!
802019.main: Commander, did you know that the most important thing in dance is not the technique, but rather the confidence? Yes, the confidence that "I am at my very best on stage!" |The dances of the Sakura Empire, in contrast to my passionate and free-flowing form, focus more on tradition. C'est magnifique! |Recently, more and more people have become interested in dance. Commander, you should join as well!
802019.unlock: Émile Bertin, retrofit complete! I feel like a completely new person! To show my gratitude, Commander, I'll perform a brand new dance for you!
802019.drop_descrip: Émile Bertin, retrofit complete! I feel like a completely new person! To show my gratitude, Commander, I'll perform a brand new dance for you!
802019.touch2: Commander, you need to focus more when you're dancing!
802019.home: Allow me to restore your energy with my dance, Commander!
802019.expedition: I'll head down to the docks to dance a little for the girls who are coming back~

10600061.detail: Your port is quite fine. With hot springs and beaches, there are plenty a wonderful place to choose... This looks to be quite the auspicious vacation, indeed, ah-haha.
10600061.touch: Hehe, I wouldn't mind it if you... came closer.
10600061.login: What are you doing, standing there like a fool? Don't hold back, come closer... to my side.
10600061.main: More than me, you seem to be the one direly in need of a vacation.|Hehehe, Commander, won't you join me for a drink under these beautiful, crimson leaves?|What are you looking at? If there's something that interests you... shouldn't you take a closer look? Ah-haha.
10600061.unlock: Oho! To think there was a place with this much class... Not bad! I shall hereby be enjoying my hot springs vacation right here, hehehe.
10600061.drop_descrip: Oho! To think there was a place with this much class... Not bad! I shall hereby be enjoying my hot springs vacation right here, hehehe.
10600061.home: You, leaving me alone like this... Come take the place of this monkey, hurry in to the bath.

900277.detail: There are many Royal Navy ships named "Eagle," and I will go great lengths to maintain its honourable reputation.
900277.touch: What is it? An invitation to get lunch? Hmm... Sorry, but could you go in my place?
900277.login: Great to see you! Based upon your punctuality, I can already tell that you're a responsible commander.
900277.battle: The battlefield... Heh, I'm getting all fired up!
900277.hp_warning: A warrior of the Royal Navy won't back down so easily!
900277.feeling2: People say I'm not great at socializing, a fact that I begrudge. But my social skills aside, I do know my manners.
900277.mission_complete: Now that's the face of an accomplished commander. Good job.
900277.feeling5: You are irreplaceable to me. Whatever becomes of me... Scratch that. I'll stay the way I am now, just for you. Because I think this is what made me equally irreplaceable to you. Am I right?
900277.upgrade: Enhancements, huh... I just wish they wouldn't affect my weight...
900277.unlock: The name is Eagle. I intend to serve your fleet to the utmost of my abilities as a proud warrior of the Royal Navy.
900277.feeling4: Despite my low-calorie diet and daily rigorous exercise, my weight stays the same... *sigh*, I guess my past status as a battleship defines me more than I think... But why?! How does everyone else manage to lose weight just fine?!
900277.feeling1: You're betraying everyone's trust in you by acting like this. Pull yourself together, for god's sake!
900277.propose: I once met my final obstacle in the Suez Canal... But if you ever need saving, I will overcome any obstacle to get to you, Commander. This is my promise not just as a warrior, but as your lover.
900277.drop_descrip: Eagle-class light aircraft carrier – Eagle (HMS Eagle.)
900277.touch2: You see, this is the reason why we have to teach people proper etiquette.
900277.mission: There's still unfinished missions, Commander. We should get them done sooner rather than later.
900277.home: My body weight's still the same as it w– Oh! Commander! Didn't think you'd be back so soon. A-anyway, you'd better give our next mission plan a look!
900277.win_mvp: To show compassion to your foe is to put the safety of your allies at risk.
900277.expedition: Commission complete. Let's go and offer the returning team some biscuits. Don't worry about me, I can do without.
couple_encourage: Let us fight side by side!
Hrmh! Try as you wish, you won't beat me!
900277.mail: There's mail for you. Don't forget to give it a look.
900277.lose: Tsk, I've taken damage after fighting for so long... I'll need repairs when we return.

10700020.detail: Is there something you need me for? I was just about to start practicing singing though...
10700020.touch: I'm sorry... I'd like to do some vocal exercises to warm up my voice...
10700020.login: Good morning to you, Commander. I'd like to go over today's schedule with you, if you don't mind.
10700020.battle: I'm all done warming up and ready to sing!
10700020.feeling2: Lalala~♪ Oh, Commander. I was just warming up my voice.
10700020.mission_complete: It looks like you've finished up the rest of your work. Well, I'll be getting back to practicing singing.
10700020.main: If there's nothing you need me to do, can I read some sheet music to pass the time? I'd like to practice the songs I'm singing at my next performance.|The people at this port all operate such huge machinery... It's very impressive. I'm not very good with machines, you see.|Lalala~♪ No, I need to put a bit more emotion into this part... Oh, Commander. I'm sorry, I'm having a hard time understanding this song...
10700020.feeling5: Um, Commander, would you mind accompanying me for a little bit? I've been practicing a new song, but I've been stuck on a part. I was hoping to get your opinion.
10700020.upgrade: Thank you very much. This has been an invaluable experience for me.
10700020.unlock: Pleased to meet you. My name is Chihaya Kisaragi. Are you the one in charge of this port? I look forward to working with you.
10700020.feeling4: There are a lot of children here at the port. You know, I've been teaching some of them how to sing at their request. Hehe, everyone has such pretty singing voices.
10700020.propose: Having come here and been able to sing for many people... I consider this a very valuable experience. To express my feelings for the Commander who gave me this opportunity... I'd like to sing you a song!
10700020.drop_descrip: Pleased to meet you. My name is Chihaya Kisaragi. Are you the one in charge of this port? I look forward to working with you.
10700020.skill: Let this song... reach the hearts of everyone!
10700020.profile: My name is Chihaya Kisaragi. I aim to become a singer that's on a higher level than anyone else. You... want me to sing for you? Well... just one song then.
10700020.touch2: P-please stop. Where do you think you're touching me!
10700020.mission: It looks like there's still work left to be done.
10700020.home: Good work, Commander. Will... you be taking a short break? Understood.
10700020.win_mvp: It's a victory. But I'm still a long way from reaching the top...
10700020.expedition: Commander, it seems like people are back from commissions. Shouldn't we go and greet them?
couple_encourage: Haruka! Let us sing together!
Azusa, let us do our best.
10700020.mail: Commander, we've received some mail. I think it's a good idea to go check it soon.
10700020.feeling3: An idol's work isn't limited to only singing. However, improving your singing skills will aid in any job... That's what I think.
10700020.lose: ...Ugh! If only I had practiced singing a bit more...

202211.detail: This outfit's design is rather bold... I'm more accustomed to my maid uniform...
202211.touch: Commander, you want to rest in my lap? If you'd like, go ahead~
202211.login: Commander, it's been a long time since you've been able to enjoy a moment of rest, hasn't it?
202211.main: My obligations as a maid do not end when I am not in my uniform. If you need anything, just let me know. |Everyone is busy with Spring Festival preparations... but I'd like to take this opportunity to slack off a little~ |You'd like to know if there are any secrets behind the Dragon Empery's culinary and artistic crafts? Hehe, stay tuned~
202211.unlock: As I am but a maid, it is a great honor to be able to wear such a gorgeous outfit… How do I look, Commander? "Not sure where to start feasting your eyes?" Oh my... Commander...
202211.drop_descrip: As I am but a maid, it is a great honor to be able to wear such a gorgeous outfit… How do I look, Commander? "Not sure where to start feasting your eyes?" Oh my... Commander...
202211.touch2: Commander, I see that you've also become quite bold.
202211.home: Holidays in the Dragon Empery seem to have a lot of complicated customs. Perhaps they are comparable with a Royal maid's code of etiquette? Hehe~

301621.detail: Would you like to go to the beach with us, Commander? I want to build sandcastles with everyone!
301621.login: Commander, do you know where my sisters are? We promised we'd go to the beach, together...
301621.main: Ugh... I want to invite Yukikaze, but... she's hard to approach...|Commander, are my life jacket and float ring in order?|We're going to the beach... so Isokaze shouldn't ask me to play warring states with her, hopefully...
301621.unlock: The butterfly flew... Huh? Where did it...? Hamakaze? Hamakaze?! Huh? Where are Urakaze and Isokaze? Where did...? We said we'd all go to the beach, so where did they go...?
301621.drop_descrip: The butterfly flew... Huh? Where did it...? Hamakaze? Hamakaze?! Huh? Where are Urakaze and Isokaze? Where did...? We said we'd all go to the beach, so where did they go...?
301621.home: Commander, are you ready to go to the beach?
301621.win_mvp: Ugh... I was just trying to get to the beach...

900276.detail: The big mirror in my room? What about it? If I told you, "I just like mirrors," would that satisfy your curiosity?
900276.touch: Maybe try finishing your work before you "chat me up" or "interview me" or however you wanna sugarcoat it?
900276.login: There's some saying that goes, "the early bird catches the worm." ...If that's true, I guess you'd starve, Commander.
900276.battle: Careful, now. The battlefield is no place to worry about fuel economy.
900276.hp_warning: ...I can't afford to mess around, huh.
900276.feeling2: I can hear just fine, Commander, so don't go yelling in my ear, thanks...
900276.mission_complete: Those mission rewards will expire if you don't claim them. Maybe.
900276.feeling5: How would I describe you? I dunno, I guess like a storm in the middle of a peaceful voyage... No, no, I didn't mean it like that... Sorry, what I meant to say is, um...
900276.upgrade: Thanks a bunch... Well, yeah, didn't you want a thank-you?
900276.unlock: I'm Perseus, from the Royal Navy. You can pronounce it "Per-see-us" if you want though... Well, whatever. Are we done here? Great. Nice meeting you.
900276.feeling4: I'm a total moron... Why am I so rude to the Commander when I just want to be friends... I'm so, so stupid...
900276.feeling1: You really are like a can of rancid surstr?mming.
900276.propose: Obviously I don't hate you, Commander. How could I, when I adore talking to you and being patted on the head? L-look, I'm trying to say... I love you. I mean it...
900276.drop_descrip: Colossus-class light aircraft carrier – Perseus (HMS Perseus.)
900276.touch2: You must really want a seat at the naval jailhouse dinner table, huh?
900276.mission: What kind of lazy cat are you, just lounging around all day instead of doing missions?
900276.home: One quick battle, and you're knackered already, Commander? You have the stamina of a beached whale.
900276.win_mvp: Looks like the enemy will have to, uh, try harder next time.
900276.expedition: Look, Commander... No, I'm not angry, I was just going to tell you a commission is done.
couple_encourage: Time for a new experiment?
900276.mail: You've got mail. Nope, didn't bring it with me. Next time, ask, and I'll consider it.
900276.feeling3: If you ask me, people should be able to say whatever they want... Oh, hello there, Commander. Just talking to myself.

408084.detail: I lost to Bulldog again... Commander, it's time for special trainiiing. We'll doodle her face into oblivion.
408084.touch: I'm no bunny, I'm a shaaark. A scary shark that'll bite yooou. Raaawr.
408084.login: New Year's is a lucky daaay. I'll get lots of swirly-whirlieees. Do you have any, Commander?
408084.main: Everyone's talking about their year-first dreams... I dreamed I turned into a big shark. Raaawr.|I've got you a New Year's card with encrypted teeext. I can decipher it for yooou.|Bulldog drew the art on my paddle. She's a really good artist.
408084.unlock: Commander, happy new yeeear. I'm no bunny, I'm a shaaark. Not a cute shark, but a crimson, scaaary shark. Raaawr.
408084.drop_descrip: Commander, happy new yeeear. I'm no bunny, I'm a shaaark. Not a cute shark, but a crimson, scaaary shark. Raaawr.
408084.home: Let's build a snowman. Or a shiver of snowshaaarks. ...There's no such thing as a snowshark?

801030.detail: Everyone here is so nice... but, there are some who seem hard to strike up a conversation with...
801030.login: Vas-y! Come on, the day's work is only beginning!
801030.feeling2: I'm gonna take a stroll around the port today~♪ Maybe I can make some new friends!
801030.mission_complete: Yay, the mission rewards are here! Huh...? We still have to check them?
801030.main: I made friends from several different camps yesterday! Ehehe~♪ |Ah, those are the girls I played with yesterday! Commander, I'm going to get up for a bit! |If everyone all got along, then we wouldn't have any wars!
801030.feeling5: A relationship more important than friendship... lovers? But, I don't know what it means to be lovers... Huh? Just do what we always do?
801030.unlock: I've finally found you! Commander, it's a pleasure to meet you! Um, my name...? Ah! I'm Le Téméraire, a Le Hardi-class destroyer from Iris Libre!
801030.feeling4: Commander, even though I've made a lot of friends, you're... something special. That's because I'm happiest when I'm with you!
801030.feeling1: Commander, you're not going to have any friends left!
801030.propose: I'm not sure what this "marriage" thing is all about, but surely it means that we'll always be together from now on! Mmhm! I'll always be at your side, Commander!
801030.profile: I am the Le Hardi-class destroyer, Le Téméraire! I was never completed during that war, but I'm really happy that I can be with all of you now!
801030.touch2: W-wait, I'm not emotionally prepared yet!
801030.mission: We still have missions left! Let's knock them out in one go!
801030.home: Welcome back! I put the documents back on the shelves for you! ...Huh? You still wanted to check those?
801030.win_mvp: Heheh~ Did you see me just now?
801030.expedition: Commander, I'm going to go welcome back the girls who are coming back from their commissions!
couple_encourage: Miss Dunkerque, I'd like a macaron!
801030.mail: Mail's here! I already opened it for you!
801030.feeling3: I have a play date with my friends today! Commander, want to join us?

301650.detail: Commander? If there's anything you want me to do, please let me know. I love helping out.
301650.touch: What's wrong, Commander? Are you tired? Thirsty? Hungry? Aaanything you need, I'll take care of it.
301650.login: Oh, hello. Do we have everything we'll need today? Better make sure.
301650.battle: I don't want to lose any friends today!
301650.hp_warning: Everyone... just a little bit longer...!
301650.feeling2: Commander, can I give you a hand with anything? Any little old thing? Really, I can do aaaaaanything♪
301650.mission_complete: Commander? The mission rewards have been delivered!
301650.main: Laa laa laa ♪ It's another beautiful day today, Commander!|What should I make for the girls today... Any ideas, Commander?|It's great seeing all the happy faces here every day. I truly love it here♪
301650.feeling5: I'm not taking care of myself...? Commander, you're such a worrywart... Since you're so concerned about me, can I ask you for a favor? Commander, I want you to promise me you'll aaalways be with me, forever and ever...
301650.upgrade: Now I'll be able to protect everyone.
301650.unlock: Petaaals of the saaaakuuuraaa... Oh, hello, Commander. Nice to meet you. I'm Michishio. It's a pleasure.
301650.feeling4: Helping people makes me happy. Hm? You don't want me to overdo it? You're worried about me after all, Commander~
301650.feeling1: I don't think I can be friends with you, Commander...
301650.propose: I've never been so happy before... But I know today is just the start of an even happier life, isn't it? It definitely is, isn't it, Commander♪
301650.profile: I'm the third ship of the Asashio-class, Michishio. I was part of the 8th and 24th Destroyer Squadrons, until finally I was assigned to the 4th Destroyer Squadron. That's when I joined the Battle of Leyte Gulf... Hmm, even though I'm pretty unlucky, I'm hoping everyone here will still be my friend!
301650.mission: Commander, I'm putting the new mission documents right here, okay?
301650.win_mvp: B-but everyone pitched in... Um, I'm... I just, everyone's looking at meee!
301650.expedition: Commander, shouldn't we go out to meet the girls you sent out on commission? It's about time for them to be getting back.
301650.feeling3: I've lost a lot of friends over the years... Asashio and them, Suzukaze, Umikaze... I'm so afraid to lose any more... I'll do anything for my friends...
301650.lose: Wait! Please don't leave me heeere!

900271.detail: Commander, why are you staring at me...?
900271.touch: ...Don't think I'm upset just because I have little to say. Just let me know if you need anything.
900271.login: We're in a state of emergency. Be prepared to run the Holiday Express, even if it's a holiday.
900271.battle: Why did they choose to become our enemy...?!
900271.feeling2: There is no beauty in warfare. There is only ugliness in the suffering and loss of life we inflict upon each other.
900271.mission_complete: There are a ton of rewards? Of course.
900271.main: Right now, another place out there is being engulfed by the flames of war...|Eldridge's ability? I'm not exactly sure, but... I feel like I've seen it somewhere... |All resistance is meaningless before the Essex-class's attack formation.
900271.feeling5: We were born as weapons of warfare, and I thought that is all we would ever be. But having spent time with you, I'm beginning to think... that there's more to our lives than war.
900271.unlock: Bunker Hill, one of the Essex-class carriers, is joining the fleet under your command. Don't worry, you'll see the extent of my abilities soon enough.
900271.feeling4: Something strange has been going on with my thoughts recently. Whenever I start thinking about things, your face pops up in my head and makes it hard for me to stay calm...
900271.feeling1: I'd rather not talk to you right now.
900271.propose: Sorry... My mind has gone completely blank... I'm lost for words... Oh, that's right! "I pledge loyalty and love to you until the end of time." ...How does that sound?
900271.drop_descrip: Essex-class aircraft carrier – Bunker Hill, Hull Number CV-17.
900271.profile: Essex-class, Bunker Hill. My name comes from a battlefield in the Revolutionary War. I've seen my fair share of battles... and know that war brings nothing but sorrow and pain. Let's not talk about it any more.
900271.touch2: By the looks of things, you won't learn your lesson without some harder-hitting "experience."
900271.mission: Missions... should best be completed in a timely manner.
900271.home: You've returned? ...Very well. Why don't we prepare for the next sortie?
900271.win_mvp: So this is the end that you all chose...
900271.expedition: Pardon, but I'll go greet the girls who are coming back from their commission. Just wait here until I report back.
couple_encourage: You are nothing before the Essex class.
Project Rainbow? ...It has a nice ring to it...
900271.mail: The mail's here... Wonder if there's any new intel?
900271.feeling3: Don't think I'm upset just because I have little to say. If anything, I'm probably thinking about something, or about how to express myself.
900271.lose: Their power... surpasses even the "Dragon's Jaws"...?

304051.detail: Is there anything I would like to tell Akagi? Of course, I have many things I would like to impart with her, but perhaps it would be more appropriate that she hears those words from you, Commander. And perhaps, that would be the more interesting way of doing things... Don't you agree? Hehe~
304051.touch: I'm not going anywhere, Commander. That's what you and Akagi wished for, after all.
304051.login: Commander, are you not going to head down to the ocean? There is no need to worry about me, so please enjoy your time with the others.
304051.battle: First, let us assemble our formation.
304051.mission_complete: The mission rewards have arrived. Please look over them.
304051.main: Kaga's younger sister is quite skilled at drawing... As for my sister, well... Akagi has her own charming points~|I'm sorry for the trouble I've caused you due to my less than ideal health, but I would like to say... Commander, you have my deepest gratitude for looking after me all this time.|Would a light meal be to your liking, Commander? Kaga, Akagi, and I worked together to make this. We chose our dishes assuming that you would also be here to partake in our cooking. Hehe~
304051.unlock: Commander, are you here to pay me a visit? ...Ah, there is no need to be concerned about me. I made a promise to both you and Akagi that I would be mindful of my health.
304051.drop_descrip: Commander, are you here to pay me a visit? ...Ah, there is no need to be concerned about me. I made a promise to both you and Akagi that I would be mindful of my health.
304051.touch2: Commander, I would advise you to pay closer attention to your surroundings before doing things like this...
304051.mission: Please entrust this assignment to Amagi.
304051.home: Thank goodness you're back. Everyone here at port was waiting for your safe return, Commander.
304051.expedition: Commander, a commission has been completed. Shall I summon the returnees here once they are finished with their preparations?
304051.mail: New mail has arrived — yes, it's good news. You need not be concerned.
304051.lose: *cough* *cough*... I wonder if I am coming down with a cold...

801029.touch: Commander, are you trying to see what's different about me?
801029.battle: In order to protect everything that we cherish!
801029.main: Looks like there are plenty of folks in the Sakura Empire who understand the way of the sword. I'd love to meet with them sometime. |I still fall short compared to the other knights, but I'm in no rush. Slowly but surely, I know I'll be able to catch up to them. |Hnn! Haah! Oh... I started swinging my sword again without even realizing it...
801029.unlock: My hard work has finally paid off! Commander, thank you for your guidance all this time! I'll return the favor by bringing you even more honors in battle!
801029.drop_descrip: My hard work has finally paid off! Commander, thank you for your guidance all this time! I'll return the favor by bringing you even more honors in battle!
801029.touch2: Hey, there's nothing different about that place... Are you doing this on purpose?!
801029.win_mvp: I'll say it again. I won't let Commander's efforts go to waste!

900270.detail: One should always go all out, no matter the enemy... Having that said, there are various practical reasons why that isn't always possible...
900270.touch: Want something to drink? Then, how about a martini – shaken, not stirred? Just kidding!
900270.login: Am I slated to sortie today? If not, hurry up and fix that!
900270.battle: Flight preparations complete! Attack squadrons, roll out!
900270.hp_warning: Crap, I didn't think there'd be so many of them...
900270.feeling2: The great symbol of fearlessness is none other than I – Intrepid! Don't you forget that!
900270.headtouch: Wooahh?! You're messing up my hair?!
900270.mission_complete: Mission accomplished! See, there's nothing you can't do if you put your mind to it!
900270.feeling5: The stars in the night sky are distant. So distant that even with all the courage in the world, the effort it would take to reach them is unfathomable... However, all it takes to catch the commander in front of me is.... this! Hehe, isn't that right?
900270.upgrade: I feel like I can always keep improving! For example, how 'bout giving me a dozen jets?
900270.unlock: "The Fighting I" of the Essex-class, Intrepid, is here! Commander, leave the combat missions to me! I'll bring home victory and glory!
900270.feeling4: During my free time, I like to read, watch movies, or stargaze. Oh, by the way, I got a movie ticket from Casablanca. Why don't we go watch it?
900270.feeling1: Commander, the way you're acting now makes you no different from a coward!
900270.propose: I didn't expect you to be the one to take the initiative... but I suppose that's fine too. Commander, guess I'll continue to be in your care then! As long as I am with you, I want you to push forward and face the future fearlessly!
900270.drop_descrip: Essex-class aircraft carrier – Intrepid, Hull Number CV-11.
900270.profile: I'm the third ship of the Essex class, Intrepid! Although my poor luck during the war earned me quite a few unflattering nicknames... Heheh, that's all behind me now! Commander, under your command, I'll show you just how powerful I am!
900270.touch2: You... *sigh*...I'm way more inclined to beat you to a pulp than to praise you for your bravery.
900270.mission: Having trouble with your missions? If you're stumped, why don't you let me try my hand?
900270.home: Phew, I'm back! Oh, you need a battle report, repair and resupply overviews, and a mission debriefing? Sure, five minutes should be enough, right? After that, send me back out there!
900270.win_mvp: The crown of victory goes to me, the one who knows no fear!
900270.expedition: Commission completed, resources received~! Hehe, way to go, Commander. You know exactly how important logistics are to our fleet operations!
couple_encourage: Task Force 38, let's rock and roll!
900270.mail: There's new mail... do we have new orders?
900270.feeling3: Oh, Commander! This– yeowwwch! Who decided it was a good idea to leave a trolley here?! Jeez, why does this always happen to me...Ah, um, nevermind, I'm fine! More importantly, when do I get to sortie?
900270.lose: I have to go to the docks again...? Damnit, why is it always me... Y-you didn't hear anything!

301059.battle: It will be all right, Commander... Believe in me...
301059.main: Commander, I feel like I can work a bit harder when I'm with you...|Being with everyone makes me happy... so I want to be able to stay together...|Commander, if you leave me alone... I'll be hurt...
301059.unlock: Ayanami, retrofit complete. I feel stronger, yes... Having that said, Commander, can you pat my head? I want to be pampered a bit...
301059.drop_descrip: Ayanami, retrofit complete. I feel stronger, yes... Having that said, Commander, can you pat my head? I want to be spoiled a bit...
301059.win_mvp: If it is for everyone's sake... I am willing to become the "Demon."

312012.detail: Nya...aah?! This outfit... puts me way over budget! I'm going to have to think of some new promotions, nya... Commander?! H-how can I help you, nya?
312012.touch: Akashi earned all these gems here through hard work! Commander, I'm just letting you see them to motivate you, nya~♪
312012.login: Commander, how can I help you, nya~
312012.main: There sure are a lot of people at this party, nya. Maybe I should open up a booth here, nya. |Since this celebration is such a special occasion, maybe I could afford to cut you a little discount, nya~ |Commander, would you like some gems? Or maybe some wisdom cubes, nya? Or... maybe a generous bit of both, nya?
312012.feeling5: Commander, Akashi wants a lap pillow, nya! ...The other way around? No way, nya! Akashi wants to curl up in your lap, nya!
312012.unlock: Heheh, this is what I've been saving up for, nya~♪ A special dress that combines Gothic fashion with Sakura charm! Commander, how about those gems, nya?
312012.drop_descrip: Heheh, this is what I've been saving up for, nya~♪ A special dress that combines Gothic fashion with Sakura charm! Commander, how about those gems, nya?
312012.touch2: This place is locked behind a paywall, nya! Um... fifty gems per time, nya!
312012.home: While everyone was hard at work outside, Akashi helped to set up the party, nya~

801032.detail: I got this lollipop from Mutsuki earlier! Oh, and keep it a secret from Dunkerque, okay? I'm hoping she'll make one for me later~
801032.touch: This Manjuu plushie is so squishy! It feels super comfy to cuddle with!
801032.login: Nighty night, Commander! ...It's not time to sleep yet, though! Feeling cheated? Hehehe~
801032.main: I can't sleep now, there's still tons of stuff I wanna do before bed. No staying up late allowed? Aww... Fine, then I'll lie down right now!|Today was so much fun! I bet tomorrow will be even more fun, Commander!|Hang on, where's my Manjuu plushie gone? Oh! It was hiding in the pillow!
801032.unlock: How do I look? These pajamas are super cute, aren't they? Ehehe, I really like this one! It even matches with Opiniâtre's!
801032.drop_descrip: How do I look? These pajamas are super cute, aren't they? Ehehe, I really like this one! It even matches with Opiniâtre's!
801032.touch2: Th-th-th-that's not something you should be squishing...!
801032.home: Welcome back, Commander! Watch out, Manjuu plushie coming at you! Hehehe~ Smells nice, doesn't it?

301850.detail: All you do is loaf around in here... Are you a commander, or a deadbeat?
301850.touch: Whuah! Would you STOP tickling me?
301850.login: You came of your own accord. How fortunate... Never you mind. Get to work.
301850.hp_warning: When push comes to shove, retaliate...!
301850.feeling2: What do you need from me? Make it quick.
301850.headtouch: What the–?! K-k-keep your hands off my ears!
301850.mission_complete: Mission complete. Will you get a move on already and process the rewards?
301850.main: How, I wonder, would one go about making Agano stop touching my ears...|Urgh... Reading so much fine print text has given me a headache. Commander, requesting permission to rest...|I like the quiet of the office, free from the jarring hum of propeller aircraft.
301850.feeling5: All your talk of attendants and "hanging out" was just an attempt to seduce me, was it not? N-no, I mean nothing bad by it! Oh, forget it! You toyed with my heart, and now you must o-own up to it!
301850.unlock: I am Kamikaze-class destroyer Oite, assuming my post starting today. I will perform my duties, and anything beyond that I will decide on a case-by-case basis. End of report.
301850.feeling4: I cannot wrap my head around your need for an attendant when there are no hostiles at the port... Nor do I grasp this "hang out" business! Although I did enjoy our friendly exchange! E-e-end of report!
301850.feeling1: I expect no betterment from you. Go on, let your name be irreversibly tarnished.
301850.propose: I don't know what to do at this ceremony! You insisted on it, so it's your responsibility to g-guide me through it! E-end of report...
301850.profile: I served as flagship of Destroyer Division 29 within Destroyer Squadron 6. I performed various escort and transport missions. Leave any tasks of this nature to me. End of report.
301850.touch2: Whuah?! Wh-wh-wha-what has gotten into you, fool?!
301850.mission: To think a trivial task would have you up-ended like this... If you so insist it's impossible, then I will set an example.
301850.home: No unauthorized persons entered the office in your absence. End of report.
301850.win_mvp: All I did was perform my duty, as I said I would.
301850.expedition: The commission team has returned. I will see to the transport of the goods, and you to its inspection.
couple_encourage: I have you covered!
301850.mail: Correspondence has arrived. Don't come nagging later, saying I didn't inform you.
301850.feeling3: You need an attendant for your outing? Understoo– Wait, why would you need an attendant for a tour of your own port? ...You want to "hang out" with me? What does that mean?
301850.lose: We must start anew at boot camp...

900273.detail: An improvement in operational code and tactical variables... This sequence should be useful. I shall write this down in my notebook.
900273.touch: I am right here, Commander. Do not hesitate to give me your orders.
900273.login: Here is today's schedule, Commander. Read it at your leisure.
900273.battle: Now, as outlined in our briefing, prepare for combat!
900273.hp_warning: I have sustained damage, but it is under control...
900273.feeling2: Are you curious about this book? It is just a notepad, more or less. Rest assured, there is nothing remarkable about it. And it is certainly not something you need look at.
900273.mission_complete: A mission has been completed. That's one burden off our minds.
900273.feeling5: Commander, all of today's clerical tasks have been completed right on schedule. This is a good opportunity to... Indeed, as you've requested, I will teach you about the so-called "sacrament of love."
900273.upgrade: Your kindness will not go unrewarded, Commander.
900273.unlock: Béarn, Iris Libre's very first aircraft carrier, reporting for duty. It is an honor to fight by your side. I eagerly await your orders, Commander.
900273.feeling4: This "grimoire" topic again? I do not appreciate your insistence on it. "A sacrament from the Iris Libre can perform all sorts of miracles"... Assuming that were even true, how would you utilize such great power, Commander?
900273.feeling1: "You are the most outstanding, exceptional commander I have ever met." – You can only hope to hear me say these words in your most outlandish dreams.
900273.profile: My name is Béarn, I am the Iris Libre's first aircraft carrier, converted from the unfinished 5th Normandie-class dreadnought. I lived to see the end of the strife between Iris and Vichya... A tragedy I pray will never happen again.
900273.touch2: Do you lack the knowledge of what being a decent person entails, or are you simply unable to control yourself, Commander?
900273.mission: Commander, I have received word of new mission directives from headquarters. I shall go and make some arrangements.
900273.home: You would like something sugary in preparation for your mental labor? It so happens I have a list of our stock of confectionaries. Please have a look.
900273.win_mvp: How would you say I did? Was my performance satisfactory?
900273.expedition: Transport commissions and cargo escorts are vital, of course, but let's not forget the important safety of our docks.
couple_encourage: I'd love to transport fascinating items with you.
I am profoundly honored to fight by your side.
Allow me to show you an Iris sacrament.
900273.mail: Reporting in. I have a newly arrived letter for you, Commander.
900273.feeling3: A "grimoire"? Hmm... And you say L'Opini?tre told you this? It's certainly an amusing allegory. Now, I'm afraid I must take my leave for a while, as I have business to attend to.
900273.lose: I sincerely apologize, Commander. I take full responsibility for this defeat.

301602.drop_descrip: General! I, Isokaze, have done my utmost to prepare the equipment! Now, with Lord Urakaze's presence, our Sengoku☆War-Band is complete! Of course, you are more than welcome to join our ranks, General!

801031.detail: Commander, what do you think about my choice of swimsuit...? Ah, by the way, I also picked out Opiniâtre's swimsuit!
801031.touch: The sea is refreshing and feels great! Commander, you should come on in as well!
801031.main: Today's the day of the big beach volleyball meet! My friends and I are aiming for the top spot!|Opiniâtre, are you busy practicing your "magic" again? Since we came all the way out here, you might as well have some fun... |Huh, a crab? ...Ehh?? It was just right there... Where'd it run off to?
801031.feeling5: I had a great time today! Ehehe~♪ But you know, it'd be nice to have some alone time with you, Commander... Hey, umm, can I... lean against your shoulder...?
801031.unlock: Commander, I've finished changing into my swimsuit! Heheh~ let's head down to the beach and enjoy ourselves as much as we can!
801031.drop_descrip: Commander, I've finished changing into my swimsuit! Heheh~ let's head down to the beach and enjoy ourselves as much as we can!
801031.touch2: Awawawa! Th-the strings are coming loose...!
801031.mission: Huh? We're getting work on our day off?
801031.home: Commander, aren't you hot...? Mm! Here, have an ice pop!

299040.detail: All great odysseys must begin somewhere, but true glory only awaits those who reach their destination... That's why you ought to stay your course until the very end!
299040.touch: I tend to get along better with people who are straightforward. If there's something you want to say to me, say it clearly.
299040.login: You've finally come. What should we start with today? It's great to think about battle plans and all, but how about sending me on a sortie first?
299040.battle: Alright, let's do this with fanfare!
299040.feeling2: Everything goes on the battlefield. Whether you fight fair-and-square or use backhanded methods, it matters not. History is written by the victors.
299040.mission_complete: Can't complain about the bounty, but I just feel like there's "something" missing.
299040.main: Basically, ships arm themselves with armor and equipment—in other words, with artillery and torpedoes. Meanwhile, humans arm themselves with courage and intelligence—in other words, with perception and wisdom.|While I don't hate customs and ceremony, I do prefer the simpler things.|The dew-kissed fruit of the morning makes for the best juice. Don't you agree?
299040.feeling5: I see. So what you're telling me is that it's not the place that matters, but that if I'm with you, anywhere is fine? ... Haha... W-Wait... are you saying...
299040.upgrade: Now that's the kind of sound I want to hear from my main guns! Ahahaha!
299040.unlock: So you're the Commander? Seems you've got some backbone. I'm the Royal Navy heavy cruiser, Drake, and I'll be joining your fleet. Just making sure, you will deploy me, right?
299040.feeling4: Sure, it's great to travel together and all, but aren't all these places too close by? Port, the surrounding areas, and the nearby ocean... Sigh. Honestly, going to these places doesn't make me excited at all. Next time, I'm taking you somewhere farther away.
299040.feeling1: I am willing to turn a blind eye to a few accidents, but if you keep doing this intentionally, don't expect any mercy from me.
299040.propose: Don't you think it's strange too? This feeling that's not quite 'having my heart stolen' or 'feeling vexed,' but more just... 'feeling embarrassed'? ...Gosh, it's all your fault that I'm not acting like myself! ... But I don't quite hate this feeling either... Well? Do you get what I mean?
299040.skill: You won't find any mercy here!
299040.profile: I'm the Royal Navy heavy cruiser, Drake. If you weren't aware of my existence before, I'll make sure you know now by showing you the power of my 9.2 inch guns!
299040.touch2: Huuh? You sure have some guts.
299040.mission: Doing mundane tasks is totally not my style. Um... Why don't we check the rewards first?
299040.home: Nice job, Commander. How would you like some fresh... grapes? Hehe, come on~ don't drop 'em!
299040.win_mvp: Victory always leaves you feeling nice and refreshed!
299040.expedition: Instead of collecting supplies like this, wouldn't it be better to just raid the enemy for... Actually, never mind.
couple_encourage: Let's see who's more useful!
299040.mail: Here, a letter for you. Anybody find information on some treasure?
299040.feeling3: Oh right, Commander. Did you have any interest in navigation... or rather, adventure? I've been recruiting mates. If you're interested, let's go look for treasure or uninhabited islands or something!
299040.lose: How humiliating... I'll get you back for this! Just you wait!

900272.detail: Place your faith in me. Follow my lead. Offer up your prayers. Seek the Lord. Only then will the path of God be opened...
900272.login: Bonjour, Commander. Please relax and drink this tea while I carry out my morning prayers.
900272.battle: All ships, prepare for combat! For liberty and glory! Aux armes, marchons!
900272.feeling2: The one you are talking to was once despisingly called many things: the calamity that brought on war, the fearsome Cardinal, and the maniac possessed by religious fervor. I ask of you: when you look at me, what do you see in me?
900272.headtouch: May Heaven confer upon you its blessings.
900272.mission_complete: The reward for those who work hard is Heaven's grace. Let us accept it gratefully.
900272.upgrade: At times, might is needed to guide others on the right path. I give you my thanks.
900272.unlock: I am Richelieu, Cardinal of Iris Libre. If you too will fight for freedom and faith, then I shall bring you victory, Commander.
900272.feeling4: You've come by again. Haven't you been getting too friendly with me? ...Just kidding. I'm truly grateful to have another person that I can chat casually with. I hope that you feel the same way, too.
900272.feeling1: Those who refuse to stop marching shall face the path of ruin... Make sure you keep that in mind.
900272.propose: As the one who guides Iris Libre, I cannot make an oath solely to you. However, I vow to protect and support you for as long as I live. This, I vow, on the holy name of Iris...
900272.touch: Please listen to our prayers closely, Commander.
900272.touch2: If nothing else, your audacity is commendable.
900272.mission: Missions may be called a kind of trial. If you take them on with the proper attitude, there is no need to worry.
900272.home: Mission complete. The fleet has safely returned to the port. Good work, Commander.
900272.win_mvp: May the wandering souls drifting about the battlefield find eternal peace and salvation... Amen...
900272.expedition: I'd like to report that the commissions have been safely completed, and that fleet operations are running smoothly. You've done a good job, Commander.
900272.mail: Letters are blessings from other people.
900272.lose: Is this... also a trial from Heaven...?

302099.touch: Commander, did you call for me?
302099.mission_complete: I brought back the rewards, Commander!
302099.main: nil|Have you finally memorized my name? Just read it out. You can give it a few tries~|My expression seems a bit softer now? It's because I like the fleet and the Commander more than I did before~!
302099.unlock: Combat retrofit complete! First Torpedo Squadron flagship, Abukuma, ready to sortie any time!
302099.drop_descrip: Combat retrofit complete! First Torpedo Squadron flagship, Abukuma, ready to sortie any time!
302099.touch2: Hey! Commander, you're going to be eating torpedoes if you keep this up!
302099.home: I've prepared snacks for everyone. Commander, there's some for you too! Come dig in!
302099.win_mvp: The most important thing is that everyone stays safe.

301831.detail: I want to be a maid who can bring happiness to everyone! ...I'm going to have to work even harder to make that happen...
301831.touch: Being able to go about business as usual in this kind of outfit is no easy feat... Real maids are truly something...
301831.login: I'll do my best to bring happiness to everyone at port, Commander! Just believe that one day, this place will be filled with happiness!
301831.main: This is the first time I've made sweets by hand. Commander, how are they? You'd like to have some more? Of course! I'll make them for you right away! |Let's emulate the Royal Maids and form the Maids of the 2nd Torpedo Squadron! What do you think, commander? |"Just spotting Naganami immediately causes one's mood to improve?" ...More weird rumors are circulating again... But if you believe that, Commander... Hehehe, I guess I'll believe it too!
301831.feeling5: Commander, your entire body is radiating happiness – I can smell it! Huh? You want to try smelling my happiness? Um, in that case, come a bit closer... Even closer...
301831.unlock: Akashi pushed me into getting this outfit, saying that it would surely make you happy, but... What do you think...?
301831.drop_descrip: Akashi pushed me into getting this outfit, saying that it would surely make you happy, but... What do you think...?
301831.touch2: Commander, at least let me set the tray down first! Eek! It's going to fall!
301831.home: Commander... Um, I mean, Master! Welcome back! Whether you want to enjoy some refreshments, or take a nap on my tail... either way is fine!

900267.detail: Know this, comrade. Even if I am battered and bruised, muddied by defeat, I will rise each time to reclaim the glory of mankind! Yes, that is the революция I desire, the only heaven that exists for me!
900267.touch: What about my rigging? Isn't fully utilizing everything at your disposal a wonderful and pragmatic ideal? Why would I consign myself to weakness for the sake of showmanship?
900267.login: Comrade, what sort of strong enemy will we face today? I, Gangut, shall stand with you!
900267.hp_warning: Ahahahaha! At last, this is a battlefield that I am meant for!
900267.feeling2: I am Battleship Gangut, also known as Oktyabrskaya Revolyutsiya. However, my name is less important the what I've achieved. Don't dwell too much on it and just call me what you want.
900267.mission_complete: Excellently done! This reward will help pave the next step of our revolution!
900267.feeling5: Let's get to the point! Comrade, I was struck by your brilliance, and thus I fell for you! And now, I face the challenge of how to express my feelings for you! Here, comrade, accept my embrace!
900267.upgrade: Comrades! You are also strong! Let our souls shine out brilliantly!
900267.unlock: Hahaha! Not bad, comrade! Come, let us fight for the safety of these azure lanes! Fight until your last breath!
900267.feeling4: Ahahahaha! Well done, comrade! No matter how strong the enemies we may face, we now join each other courageously, prepared to give everything in pursuit of greater challenges! What could be more revolutionary than that?
900267.feeling1: There is no future for those who mistake recklessness with courage, comrade.
900267.propose: A pledge, huh? While this act is symbolic in nature, it is also undeniable proof of the bonds we've formed. A toast, comrade. Please continue to guide me in the future.
900267.touch2: What are you doing, comrade? Are you not aware of how we handle lawbreakers in the Northern Parliament?
900267.mission: Missions exist for the sake of preserving the order. We should complete them as soon as possible.
900267.home: O comrade, do you return bearing news of glorious victory? Ah, but it matters not, for the thing that matters most is that you fought with all your strength!
900267.win_mvp: Rejoice, for we have earned this privilege! May this celebration become the bread that sustains us until our next victory!
900267.expedition: Hopefully our comrades will return bearing good news, unlike that bitter Ice Cruise. Come on, let's go welcome them back.
couple_encourage: Ahahaha! Finally, I have the privilege of fighting by your side, Mikasa!
For the light of revolution!
900267.mail: You have a letter, comrade. It would be best to open it soon.
900267.feeling3: I hope you don't take this the wrong way, comrade, but this fight is not just for all of us. It's also yours. Never settle with the status quo, and always seek to keep improving.
900267.lose: Comrade, consider this not a defeat, but rather a warning. A sign that we are losing sight of our revolutionary spirit.

103060.detail: Hey, Commander, please hear me out! My little sister is super duper cute!
103060.touch: Commander, Commander, please hear me out! Indy's like, sooo soft! Want to touch her together with me?
103060.login: Hey, Commander, please hear me out! My little sister is super cute!
103060.battle: ... Indy... Ah, that's not it... Everyone, follow me!
103060.mission_complete: Commander, can I use the rewards to buy snacks for Indy?
103060.main: Come on, Commander, let's head out already. Indy doesn't like people who slack around!|My little sister is just so lovely~|Would you like to see my special Indy mags?
103060.feeling5: ... Kids? Let me think... I want them to look like Indy, and... I want ten! Let's say ten to start with! ... Huh?! Aahh! Just what are you making me say~?!
103060.upgrade: Now I can do some more of this and some more of that to Indy!
103060.unlock: Nice to meet you, Commander. I'm Portland, Indy's big sister. I've participated in the battles of the Coral Sea, Midway, Guadalcanal and Santa Cruz Islands. Hm? Who's Indy? Why, it's a nickname for my dear little sister, Indianapolis!
103060.feeling4: Commander, where's that photo of Indy eating a watermelon? Ah, thank you! And the one where she's hugging a body pillow? Ah, that's where it was, thank you~! Before I knew it, you've actually gotten more familiar with my Indy collection than I have~
103060.feeling1: Don't interrupt me when I'm fantasizing about Indy!
103060.propose: It seems you and I are always appreciating just how cute Indy is, Commander... But to me, Indy still always comes first! This is the one thing I'm not giving up!
103060.drop_descrip: Portland-class Heavy Cruiser – Portland, Hull Number CA-33!
103060.skill: Aahh, Indy is sooo cute... Hey, could you stop interrupting me?
103060.profile:
I'm Portland, Indy's big sister~! Do it again, properly this time? Aww... If only they'd have called us the Indianapolis-class, rather than the Portland-class... 
I have 16 battle stars and I've participated in a few big operations too, but who cares about me? Why don't we just talk about my little sister instead?
103060.touch2: Whoa! ... Not even Indy has touched me like that before!
103060.mission: If I don't do these missions properly then I can't show myself to my little sister.
103060.home: Commander, I left an Indy plushie here, have you seen it?
103060.win_mvp: My cute little Indy~ Look! Aren't I amazing~?
103060.expedition: Commander, can I pair up with Indy for the next commission? I'll show you some cute pictures of her later!
103060.mail: I brought your mail, Commander~! What? Even I can do my job right every now and then!
103060.feeling3: Commander, do you want to see some photos of Indy when she was little? I'll show them to you even if you say no!
103060.lose: Dammit... I can't let my little sister see me like this!

101401.detail: I'm feeling a little peckish... Umm, cookies, candy, and... Ah, I musn't... I have to leave enough for Commander...
101401.login: How do you do, Commander? How's that? I learned how to curtsy from the Royal Navy maids~
101401.battle: What I saw just now could prove useful for anti-submarine operations...
101401.main: Even though I spent a lot of time training with the submarines, it's a totally different experience to enjoy the sight underwater. |This outfit was chosen painstakingly, you know? Commander, what do you think...? |Want to go see Lexington's performance together next time? I'll even get your ticket for you if you'd like.
101401.unlock: So this is an aquarium... What a novel experience! Oh, also, I won't be your guide today as it's your turn to escort me around, Commander. Please don't get us lost, okay? Ehehe~
101401.drop_descrip: So this is an aquarium... What a novel experience! Oh, also, I won't be your guide today as it's your turn to escort me around, Commander. Please don't get us lost, okay? Ehehe~
101401.touch2: Commander, did you get some perverted ideas...?
101401.win_mvp: A most graceful and elegant victory. Ehehe, thank you for your praise~

102230.detail: Someday I hope to see the sea return to its peaceful former state...
102230.touch: What is it, Commander? Was that your sortie order?
102230.login: Sortie preparations complete. Your orders, Commander?
102230.battle: Time is money, so let's strike quickly! I will lead the way!
102230.hp_warning: They have superior firepower! This may be bad...!
102230.feeling2: Being a light cruiser, I can't markedly affect the war... However, I firmly believe that the power to protect the sea rests within me.
102230.mission_complete: Mission rewards have arrived. Perhaps there is ice cream in... Oh, um, never mind that.
102230.main: Princeton... please be okay. If I had fought harder back then, things wouldn't have...|Sometimes people ridicule me for being unlucky, but having survived that hellish battle, I feel quite lucky.|I feel at ease when I'm with Cleve and my sisters. I believe this is what's known as a "bond."
102230.feeling5: A smile? Like this? That is an unusual order to issue. That is not to say I dislike it... *Giggle*
102230.upgrade: This enhancement was necessary for me to keep advancing.
102230.unlock: Starting today, Cleveland-class light cruiser Birmingham is on active duty. I will not rest until the future of the sea is secure. Commander, grant me your guidance and support.
102230.feeling4: Commander, it feels as though you have the peculiar power of calming people. Just like a peaceful sea would...
102230.feeling1: Commander, you should reflect on your actions thoroughly.
102230.propose: This must be an oath... Have we already spent this much time together, Commander...? No, I'm not displeased at all. It's just... in this case, it's... *Ahem*! Now, then... Commander, will you watch the sunrise over the horizon of the sea together with me?
102230.drop_descrip: Cleveland-class light cruiser – Birmingham, Hull Number CL-62.
102230.profile: I am Birmingham, the eighth Cleveland-class light cruiser. Born during the war, I fought to its end alongside my many sisters and earned 9 battle stars. As a Knight of the Sea, my duty continues, and I will now fight for the sea's future.
102230.mission: New mission from HQ. Let's complete it right at once, Commander.
102230.home: It is good to see you unscathed. I suggest taking a break.
102230.win_mvp: The next battleground awaits. I will stay on my guard.
102230.expedition: Every little bit counts in the end. The worth of this commission will become clear one day.
couple_encourage: Sis! I will cover your flanks!
102230.mail: Mail for you. My intuition tells me it's good news. If it's bad news, I will help you digest it.
102230.feeling3: You think I'm overly stoic...? True, but I must be in order to repel the darkness that envelops the sea.
102230.lose: What could I have done differently...

900266.detail: Is that you, Comrade Commander...? I'm afraid the office is a bit messy. But we must make sacrifices to achieve our goals.
900266.touch: You want to deepen our camaraderie? Very good, let us start by making a firm handshake part of our regular routine.
900266.login: Comrade Commander, you are late. You must not forget your proletarian values.
900266.battle: Commence bombardment! We will bury them!
900266.feeling2: Your fleet must be an iron curtain... Hm, it's a metaphorical expression... My meaning is that I hope to see this fleet stand united, just like our Northern Parliament.
900266.mission_complete: Hm? Something missing from the reward manifest...? It should be generally correct...
900266.feeling5: Gah, well done...! I have no choice but to place the pride of the Northern Parliament on the line and face defeat at the hands of Comrade Commander's charm offensive! Now then, Comrade Commander, you face the full power of my love offensive!
900266.upgrade: An excellent strengthening. The next one should be so good.
900266.unlock: I am called "Sovetskaya Rossiya," and as the mightiest of all the Northern Parliament's battleships, I am her ultimate weapon. I will press onward to eliminate all obstacles that stand between you and the Revolution.
900266.feeling4: Mm, this food is well made... Comrade Commander, thank you for serving me this meal, but I have to wonder, is this more than simple social etiquette? C- could you have some ulterior motive for this charm offensive?
900266.feeling1: This negative attitude is unacceptable. You must be forcibly reeducated.
900266.propose: So long as I draw breath, I labor to carry out my mission. Not only as a member of this fleet, but also in service of the bonds you have forged... This is not a product of rational thinking alone, but also a decision born of my subjective opinion.
900266.profile: I am Sovetskaya Rossiya, of Project 23. I was part of a strategic plan during the war, but for several reasons never came to be. I see though that I can prove my value here in this fleet with a series of decisive victories.
900266.mission: We have a mission. I will handle the clerical work. You must be clear to focus on your duties as a commander.
900266.home: Rest. And tell me now of what glorious victory you have won, or how you turn defeat to our advantage.
900266.win_mvp: Kill confirmed. You cannot stop the Northern Parliament... You cannot stop our righteous liberation!
900266.expedition: Military commissions? They are part of the logistical aspect of proper fleet management.
couple_encourage: This is no time to ponder the meaning of life. Just show us your strength!
Kirov, aid me!
900266.mail: Mail. Comrade Commander, you must read it quickly before the next one comes bringing another letter.
900266.feeling3: Comrade Commander, what is this? You wish to deepen your relationship with me as an individual, not a representative of the Northern Parliament? Well, such subjective decisions are acceptable.
900266.lose: Gah, how humiliating... to think a material defect would surface at a time like this...!

102232.detail: When snow falls over the farmlands, it kills off crop-eating insects and keeps the soil at a stable temperature. Then when the snow melts, it waters the earth... Now I can see why they call it "fruitful snow."
102232.touch: You want to... hold hands? My hands are a bit chilly, but if you don't mind that, then sure.
102232.login: Welcome back, Commander. There's snow on my umbrella? Oh, darn it. I got so absorbed in the wintry landscape that I forgot to shake the snow off.
102232.main: Princeton, I'm pretty sure that aerial maneuver you learned from Saratoga is only good for pranking people...|Ice cream doesn't melt so easily when the temperature drops. Is it weird to talk about ice cream in the middle of winter? ...Oh. Now I know...|The family all gathering to make dumplings while they chit-chat... I like the sound of this Dragon Empery tradition. It warms the heart.
102232.unlock: Happy Lunar New Year, Commander. I'm trying out Dragon Empery fashion for a change, though this dress will some getting used to. Hey, uh, do you want to join me under the umbrella? For cover against the snowfall, I mean.
102232.drop_descrip: Happy Lunar New Year, Commander. I'm trying out Dragon Empery fashion for a change, though this dress will some getting used to. Hey, uh, do you want to join me under the umbrella? For cover against the snowfall, I mean.
102232.home: Apparently tying your hair up into buns like this is the norm in the Dragon Empery... Huh? It's not?

302100.detail: Not saying anything makes you look cool? Figures... you would believe something like that.
302100.touch: You don't have to remind me, I'll get the work done.
302100.login: Welcome back. Huh? You want me to say it with more emotion? Sorry, chief. Not sure I can help with that one.
302100.battle: Fighting is a drag... but losing is an even bigger drag!
302100.hp_warning: Have I spread my misfortune to everyone...?
302100.feeling2: You must really have some strange hobbies, to want to associate with hapless folks like me. Oh well, if it's just talking... I suppose I can entertain you...
302100.mission_complete: I'll go pick up the mission rewards. Commander, you can just stay put and keep working.
302100.main: I wonder what Mikuma is doing right now... Well, I suppose there's nothing to worry about. She's not like me, after all... |Are you sure you want me to be your secretary? Just about anybody else would be better for the job. I'm serious... I'm not just saying that to avoid work. |Perhaps I should get Nachi to teach me how to be a little more cheerful... crap, hope nobody heard that...
302100.feeling5: Um... Commander, uh... maybe, umm, since you said you liked it... would you like to try... t-touching it?
302100.upgrade: Thanks... What's the matter? Am I not allowed to express gratitude?
302100.unlock: Mogami, reporting for duty... Don't worry too much about me, just leave me be and I'll find my own place to crash.
302100.feeling4: I already know that Mikuma and Nachi don't hold anything against me, but I can't forgive myself... *sigh*... Huh? My horn is cute?! ...I-idiot...
302100.feeling1: Well, a hapless fellow like me was bound to get stuck with a hapless commander...
302100.propose: Are you sure you won't regret choosing someone like me? If you say so... I suppose I can put in a bit more effort for our sake... A-anyway, please take care of me...
302100.profile: I am Mogami, nameship of the Mogami-class... on paper, anyway. After what happened to Mikuma and Nachi at Midway, I have no right to call myself that anymore... In any case, feel free to hand me your work, but just don't expect much.
302100.touch2: Eek!! Commander, are you seriously interested in someone like me...?
302100.mission: I finished organizing the task list. Even I couldn't mess something like this up... probably.
302100.home: Everyone made it back safely. Isn't that enough?
302100.win_mvp: First place, huh. Got a problem with it?
302100.expedition: You're going to go greet the commission fleet? I'll just stay here, so I don't end up ramming into someone.
couple_encourage: Mikuma, I'm sorry...
Forgive me, Nachi...
Fusou, exorcism party at your place after we're done here?
302100.mail: I picked up the mail. Can I leave it here?
302100.feeling3: My horn, huh... Well, I don't really mind, but... it kind of sticks out, doesn't it? I don't really like the attention... *sigh*...
302100.lose: So this is what I'm made of...

103130.detail: Do you want to hear my hunting stories? Alright! But which one do I start with...
103130.touch: Are you ready for the hunt?
103130.login: You have very good spirit, are you ready for today’s hunt?
103130.battle: Who will be my next prey?
103130.hp_warning: Hey, it seems like these guys are giving us a bit of trouble.
103130.feeling2: Compared to staying at port, it’s way more fun to go on a hunt! How about we plan one right away?
103130.mission_complete: Is this all the rewards... not as good as I expected.
103130.main: My war paint? Oh, I’m not the only one who does this… is this what you mean? |Torpedo? I’m not afraid of that, I was just unlucky that one time… |Hey, don’t just sit there, come with me and let’s take a look around!
103130.feeling5: After all, you are the Commander of the entire fleet. So you can’t always accompany everyday. But without you, I seem to be less motivated...
103130.upgrade: I feel my body is heating up!
103130.unlock: Hey ya! New Orleans class Heavy Cruiser, reporting in! I excel at hunting. If you have any prey that you’d like to hunt, then leave it to me!
103130.feeling4: When did you get this injury? Could it be that time when you were with me... hey, don’t move, let me help you by licking it.
103130.feeling1: It’s kinda boring talking to you...
103130.propose: It turns out that I was your prey, Commander? Even though I still am reluctant to believe it... but, I’ll hold onto Commander’s words! All-in-all, please take care of me in the future, Commander!
103130.drop_descrip: New Orleans class Heavy Cruiser— Minneapolis, hull number CA-36.
103130.profile: From the Coral Sea to Guadalcanal, I have left my footprints everywhere in the Pacific theater. Although I had to pause my mission due to little annoyances... but considering the results, my battle record can be considered as outstanding!
103130.touch2: Ya! ...you, do you want to become my prey?
103130.mission: New mission, new prey, oh boy~
103130.home: You all returned safely? That’s good to hear.
103130.win_mvp: Sorry, from the very beginning, I never intended for any of you to escape.
103130.expedition: It seems our friends have returned from the hunt.
couple_encourage: I’ll protect you this time!
To go into battle with my sisters, it’s not a bad feeling at all...
103130.mail: Urgent mission? No, turns out it was only an ordinary mail.
103130.feeling3: There’s actually a few places in port that I am interested in investigating. Let’s go and explore them now! ...Work? We can still make it on time even if we wait a bit longer!

900269.detail: What would you like to know, Commander? I'll answer to the best of my abilities.
900269.touch: Time to sortie?! Just leave it to me! Oh... you just wanted to chat...?
900269.login: There you are. I've already finished preparing everything. Commander, give us your orders!
900269.battle: All carrier-based aircraft in position, anti-air defense preparations complete. All forces, full speed ahead!
900269.feeling2: I witnessed the end of the era of battleships with my own eyes. Will carriers share the same fate some day...?
900269.mission_complete: The mission rewards have arrived. Are you sure you don't need me to go get it?
900269.feeling5: I might never be able to become a hero like Enterprise... But when I'm with you, I feel like I can do so much more than just that...
900269.upgrade: When will I be able to get jets...
900269.unlock: So this is where Enterprise is... A-ahem! I am Essex, one of the Union's state-of-the-art aircraft carriers. Commander, you can expect great things from me! I swear that I won't disappoint you!
900269.feeling4: I won't lose to anyone, not even to Enterprise. But how do I get everyone to acknowledge this? Commander, if you were in my shoes, what would you do?
900269.feeling1: I wonder how Enterprise puts up with someone like you...
900269.drop_descrip: Essex-class aircraft carrier – Essex, Hull Number CV-9.
900269.profile: I am the nameship of the Essex-class carriers. Although I was built with great expectations, I was always overshadowed by Enterprise's success. If only I could have been deployed sooner...
900269.mission: There are still unfinished missions? Mind letting me handle things this time...?
900269.home: The fleet has safely returned. Commander, I've prepared the battle report for you. Time is of the essence, so please review it right away.
900269.win_mvp: Enterprise, did you see my feat?
900269.expedition: The birth of the Essex-class would not have been possible without the hard work of the logistics teams. I have to show my gratitude to everyone.
900269.mail: There's new mail for you. Here you go.
900269.feeling3: Jealousy? No, that's not the case. Enterprise is a true hero worthy of all the respect she gets. However, compared to her dazzling aura, I'm just...
900269.lose: I won't let it end like this... I swear it!

299030.detail: The reason I adore you is because animals take the first person they see to be their lover... Uhh, I mean, their parent! Not that that's got to do with anything! You're my owner just because, and I love you just because! It's as simple as that!
299030.touch: Ahah~♡ What is it, Owner? Come on, I know you want something just from looking at your face~
