299030.login: Owneeeeer! Glomp! Squeeze! Cuddle! Sniff! What, I'm "overenthusiastic?" Well, that's just how excited I get when I see you, Owner~♡
299030.battle: What'll it be for dinner today? A plate of torpedoes, or a bowl of cannonfire?
299030.hp_warning: Meowch! It hurts, but I'm not about to let my owner down!
299030.feeling2: Where've you been, Owner? If you went to do fun stuff without inviting me then I'm gonna be a pouty tabby!
299030.headtouch: My kitty ears are a detachable hair accessory! You try 'em on too, Owner! Just for a quick moment, please, c'mon!
299030.mission_complete: Mission complete! Don't you think these tasks are a little too easy for us?
299030.main: Hey, Owner, know any funny stories about the Royal Navy? Or any other faction, that's fine! I wanna learn stuff!|I'm not a cat, okay? I might be as cuddly as a kitten, but I'm not an actual cat!|Oh, Master, would you care for some tea~? Hehehe, that was my Royal Maid impression! How was it, Owner?
299030.feeling5: If it weren't for you, I'd never have materialized in this incredible world, never made so many adorable friends, and worst of all, I never would have gotten to experience being in love with you, Owner! You're just perfect, y'know that~? Cuddly wuddly~ I love you so, so much~♡
299030.unlock: Meeeoooow! I haven't slept like that in forever! Hrm? Are you the one who woke me from my sleep? Woohoo, that makes you my owner! "Why?" Because I've totally fallen for you, duh!
299030.feeling4: Is there a chance you'll get fed up with my displays of affection, Owner? If so, I need to double down to make sure that never happens! Lemme give you a hug~♡
299030.feeling1: Hrmph... Why'd the first love of my life have to be such a disappointment?
299030.propose: Now that you've made it clear how precious I am to you, I need to respond by saying, "I love you, Owner!" a hundred times or more! Starting right now! Stay right where you are until I'm finished! Here we go! I love you, Owner!!!
299030.profile: I'm Cheshire, a heavy cruiser from the Royal Navy! Until I met you, I was just a stray in the sea of people's imagination! Which is to say, both my body and soul belong to you, Owner! Squeeeze~♡
299030.touch2: No more surprise touchies! At least tell me when you're gonna do it!
299030.mission: There's no mission we can't accomplish with our combined pawers, Owner!
299030.home: Weeelcome back, Owner! Are you okay? Gave the baddies a good beating? Didn't develop a crush on anyone else? Alrighty, then everything's all good!
299030.win_mvp: We won! See that, Owner? We wooooon! Meoww~!
299030.expedition: A commission team's back! Let's head over there and give 'em something to play with!
couple_encourage: You'll put people off if you try too hard, y'know!
Yaaay! Can I fluff you please?
I wanna learn more about being a maid!
Yaaay, it's time to partyyyy!
299030.mail: The mail's here! I wanna see what's inside! Pretty pleaseeee?
299030.feeling3: Hey, Owner! I was playing with this Sakura Empire girl earlier, and I got to touch her cat ears! REAL cat ears! Aren't you jealous? ...What? You did that ages ago? Hrmph, well there goes my brief moment of triumph!
299030.lose: Why don't we slink away before they notice?

201220.detail: (Whispers) Commander, does... does this count as a medical check up?
201220.login: Commander, welcome back! I've already prepared the documents for use today.
201220.battle: For your sake, Commander, I'll try the very best I can!
201220.feeling2: I am happy being next to you, Commander...
201220.mission_complete: I wonder what the rewards are... They must be nice!
201220.main: Uh, that... it looks like Jersey wants to play with me...|What! ...Pasta...? Th-There's none. Can I decline?|Commander, is there something I can do?
201220.feeling5: This crown? It's just a decoration. But if I'm Princess Juno, will... will you be my prince?
201220.upgrade: With this, I've become of greater use to you, Commander!
201220.unlock: Greetings, Commander. My name is Juno. Leave escort to me... I'll do my best!
201220.feeling4: I was called 'Yuno' before but, I'm not going to feel jealous you know? I'm happy just by being next to you, Commander.
201220.feeling1: Commander, have you come to dislike me...?
201220.propose: My dream... is to be your bride, Commander. Is it alright to treat this ring as your promise to me...?
201220.drop_descrip: J-class destroyer ー Juno, Hull Number F46!
201220.skill: Um... That... Juno, giving her all!
201220.profile: I'm the 4th ship of J class, Juno. Ow... My body isn't fine, so I have some small troubles, and I can't get used to fighting... But for Commander, I will work hard! So please don't be cold to me, alright?
201220.touch2: Eh... C-Commander, please don't... look at that spot...
201220.mission: New missions huh... But it's fine if you don't want to do them, right Commander?
201220.home: Commander, is there anything I can do?
201220.win_mvp: I didn't cause anyone any trouble, did I?
201220.expedition: Commander, the girls who went out for commissions have returned
201220.mail: Commander, Commander, there's new mail. Please check it!
201220.feeling3: I haven't accomplished anything huge up to this point, but it won't be a problem dealing with your surroundings, Commander!

308020.detail: Tans are a sign of good health! So why not come with me and sunbathe a bit?
308020.touch: Hm? Need any help doing your warm-ups?
308020.login: Jumpity! ... Hehe~ Did I spook you, Commander?
308020.battle: Who might be our lucky girl today~?
308020.feeling2: Commence dive! Target spotted! Fire torpedoes! Kaboooom! See? It's pretty easy! Why don't you give it a try too?
308020.mission_complete: When I see those ships coming in with our rewards, my heart shakes with the impulse to sink them... Just kidding~! I'd never do that! Hahaha, let's check out what we got!
308020.main: "What's up with my ears"? Hm? Do you wanna feel them?|Sorting paperwork... Ugh, so boring... Hey, why don't we play beach volleyball instead?|Maybe I should go for a swim~ Oh, I know! Commander, wanna have a swimming competition to see who's faster? Hehehe~
308020.feeling5: Hey, let me borrow your shoulders... Jumpity! Hehehe~ Light as a feather, right? Bring me to the office, if you will!
308020.upgrade: I wish someone would enhance my figure, too...
308020.unlock: Submarine I-26 has arrived to be your roommate from now on! Hehehe~ Let me guess: you've really been looking forward to meeting me, right?
308020.feeling4: I wonder when you'll notice that... um... that... your suit has a button loose! What were you expecting me to say? Hehehe~
308020.feeling1: Commander? Never mind, must've been the wind. Hahaha!
308020.propose: I was wondering when this day would come, but I never would've thought it'd be today... I feel so happy that I could swim 100 laps around the port! Yeah! In fact, let's go swimming right now, together!
308020.profile: Question! Which Sakura Empire submarine was the first to sink an Eagle Union merchant ship? You guessed it, this clever little cutie I-26 did! ... What happened after that, you ask? Let's leave the past behind us and focus on the present! *Giggle*
308020.touch2: What are you fantasizing about? C'mon, tell me~ Hehehe~
308020.mission: A new mission's arrived! Phew, this'll be a good chance to move around a bit!
308020.home: Huh? Commander, I think your hairline's starting to recede... Ahahaha! I'm just kidding with you!
308020.expedition: A commission's done! Put me on the team for the next one! Disrupting trade is what I do best! Hehehe~
couple_encourage: Don't be afraid! We're allies now!
Remember to do your warm-ups, or you'll get cramps, Idol of The Drydock~
308020.mail: What about your mail? It was past the deadline, so I disposed of it... Juuust kidding! Here you go, read it~
308020.feeling3: Commander, wanna see which of us can hold their breath longest? The winner gets a massage from the loser! How's that sound?

900268.detail: If you keep on peeping where you shouldn't, even kids will not be talking to you~
900268.login: Oh my~ Sorry Commander. I didn't mean to launch planes at you on purpose~
900268.battle: Two days ago it was {namecode:90}, yesterday it was {namecode:103}, and today it's you all. Let's go!
900268.mission_complete: This is bad, Commander! The mission rewards are missing! --Darn, you caught me.
900268.main: Boo! Hehe, did I susprise you?  Commander, you're slow, aren't you?!|Commander, don't confuse me with my big sister!|Eh? Call you 'big bro'? There's no way that's happening~
900268.feeling5: Commander, you dropped something~~ *kiss* ...Hehe, it was my heart?. Here, you can keep it!
900268.unlock: Hey there, and good day, Commander! I am Lexington...'s little sister, Saratoga~ If there's nothing important, I'm leaving now
900268.feeling4: Commander, I have something I want to tell you. I'm gonna write it on the back of your hand~ and done... Did you think I'm gonna write 'I like you'? Silly Commander~
900268.profile:
I am aircraft carrier Lexington's little sister, Saratoga! Hmm... I like to play pranks! But you already knew that, Commander~ 
Pioneer of aviation tactics? If my sister hadn't passed away so soon, that title would've definitely been hers.
900268.feeling1: Pranks? I already stopped pulling them on you~ You're no fun for those
900268.propose: Ah, Commander. Please wait for a bit~ The Eagle Union carriers are all gathering~ Eh? This is a once in a lifetime occassion! Despite my appearance I am a veteran. I'm well respected!
900268.drop_descrip: Lexington-class aircraft carrier ー Saratoga, Hull Number CV-3!
900268.skill: Where are you looking? I'm right over here~
900268.touch: My stature may be small, but I've yet to grow past that fact!
900268.mission: Commander, can't you complete even a mission?
900268.win_mvp: Ooh la la~ Big sis is busy, so it's fine that I get to come by once a while~
900268.expedition: Commander, my patrol planes told me the girls out for commission have returned~
900268.mail: You didn't see the mail? --Then should I read it?
900268.feeling3: Commander, what's the greatest difference between me and my big sister? The answer, is my 'color' today!
900268.lose: Oh dang~ I'll go back for repairs, and then have a good rest while I'm at it~

100020.detail: If ever in doubt, just tell me to bonk it with my hammer, bulin!
100020.touch: This bad boy is my "raison d'etre"! Be careful with it, or you'll get hurt, bulin!
100020.login: Commander, it's hammer time! You'll get super strong, bulin!
100020.battle: I'm fully charged, bulin! Let's show them what a real bulin's made of!
100020.hp_warning: Oh heck! My health bar is glowing red, bulin!
100020.feeling2: The other bulins are only one color, but I'm the whole rainbow! Which can only mean one thing: that I'm the strongest of the bunch, bulin!
100020.mission_complete: Look here! Smash that Collect All button, bulin!
100020.main: Sleepy, bulin? Then I'll charge you right up! I just need to plug in my... What? That doesn't work, bulin?|You might get a surprise when you collect 1 of each bulin! But I dunno what the surprise would even be!|My Kitty Kabam Hammer goes glimmer-glammer, sparkely sparkle, whooshy-kablam! Check it out, bulin!
100020.feeling5: I was made to upgrade fleets, nothing more, and yet you're being so kind to me... I love you, Commander! Let me give you a special type of bonk, bulin! Hm? You'd rather not?
100020.upgrade: Glad you asked, but I can't be enhanced, bulin!
100020.unlock: Bulin~! Aren't you amazed? Standing before you is the legendary secret unlockable character of the Bulin family, none other than me! Rejoice, for you have been blessed with supremely good RNG, bulin!
100020.feeling4: Are you sure you aren't hanging out with me too much, Commander? If this keeps up, the port will be in ruins soon, bulin!
100020.feeling1: You've lost your way, but don't give up! Pull yourself together, bulin!
100020.propose: Woohoo! This shiny ring is proof of our love bond, bulin! Watch this! I'm gonna whack it to infinity with my hammer! ...Never, ever whack the ring? Okay then, bulin!
100020.drop_descrip: Specialized Bulin Custom MKIII. Can be used to Limit Break all Ultra Rare ships.
100020.skill: My hammer is the hammer that will bring down the stars, bulin!
100020.profile: A wrench, a drill, and a hammer... Wait a sec! Is there some kind of pattern here, bulin?!
100020.touch2: Oh nooooooo! I'm gonna overload, bulin!
100020.mission: A new mission? A good bonk with my hammer should finish it, bulin!
100020.home: Bulin? My gear and I both need to recharge, bulin!
100020.win_mvp: My Kitty Kabam Hammer is the strongest around, bulin!
100020.expedition: Bulin! The commission team has returned with boatloads of rewards!
couple_encourage: Bulin Brigade, busting through, bulin!
Let's make 'em taste the rainbow!
100020.mail: Is it true that more mail comes in when I go "bulin"?
100020.feeling3: As thanks for always hanging with me, I'll let you borrow my Kitty Kabam Hammer for an hour, bulin! But don't use it for any mean stuff, okay?
100020.lose: My batteries are out... My Kitty Kabam Hammer was never made for battle, bulin!

306081.detail: Everyone becomes so rowdy when they get to the beach... I hope nothing bad happens today. Please, may enemy aircraft and volleyballs not come flying our way...
306081.touch: That shaved ice looks really good... I guess there's a good reason cold treats are popular in the summer.
306081.login: The sun's rays are so harsh... I should go look for some awning to hide under...
306081.main: Isuzu, who told you that...? There aren't any ghosts here, don't worry. Go out and play.|Chiyoda's quite the sore loser... She's like that even when it comes to building sand castles, so I can't even imagine how worked up she'd get over beach volleyball... If that pink-haired union girl is our opponent, I think I'll just sit out...|The weather forecast says... it'll be clear until the evening... Mmn...
306081.unlock: An order of coconut milk... and grilled sausage. Mm, that should do it. ...Hm? Commander? Are you here to place an order, or to get away from the heat?
306081.drop_descrip: An order of coconut milk... and grilled sausage. Mm, that should do it. ...Hm? Commander? Are you here to place an order, or to get away from the heat?
306081.home: Commander, you're sweating so profusely. Are you okay? ...Here's a towel. Let me wipe you down.

900132.detail: I can't rely on this thing alone...
900132.touch: Hm? I'm fine. I'm just... a little distracted.
900132.login: ... Ah, welcome back, Commander. Sorry, I was just brooding over something.
900132.battle: The enemy can't hide from me.
900132.hp_warning: SG, lock on the enemy position!
900132.feeling2: If only my recon could help the others...
900132.mission_complete: Resources are no good if they just pile up. We should make use of them.
900132.main: Are you trying to hide, Commander? No matter where you hide, I know where you are.|Commander, what should we do after the war?|If only my guns could be as strong as my radar...
900132.feeling5: I believe that you will bring us hope, Commander. This time, I'll fight to the end... Just the thought of saying goodbye to the person I love makes me feel like my heart will tear in half...
900132.upgrade: I'll use this power to protect everyone!
900132.unlock: Nice to meet you, Commander. I'm Helena. My strong suit is enemy reconnaissance. Please... guide us towards victory.
900132.feeling4: I think I've been more at ease lately... No, I was just too tense up until now. It's all thanks to the courage you've given me by being beside me.
900132.propose: A promise... from you, Commander? I see... I'm so happy...
900132.drop_descrip: Brooklyn-class Light Cruiser – Helena, Hull Number CL-50!
900132.profile: I was designed to be on par with heavy cruisers, but just my power alone isn't enough to save everyone... Commander, can you help me?
900132.touch2: If this makes you feel good, then... I'm fine with it.
900132.mission: Bit by bit we'll build the foundation for victory. We'll start by doing missions.
900132.home: Did everyone make it back safe and sound? Good. But there's spare parts lying around in the docks now... I wonder why...
900132.expedition: Hey, Commander, could I lend my SG radar to my sisters this time?
couple_encourage: Penny, cover me!
SG, full area scan! I will never let that tragedy repeat itself!
Chicky Unit... sounds kind of cute!
900132.mail: You've got new mail. It's important to stay in touch with your loved ones.
900132.feeling3: My expression? Ah... it's because I left while we were on the losing end of the war... I might just not be so used to peace and happiness. But don't worry, I'll be fine!
900132.lose: ... Please, save me... Ignore the enemy, just let them go...

900263.detail: Don't be blinded by statistics. Victory depends on far more!
900263.login: As long as I'm here, we can deal with any enemy, no matter how far they are.
900263.battle: I would never let the commander's enemies escape!
900263.hp_warning: So this is how harsh the battlefield can be.
900263.feeling2: Commander, want to hear about the history of the Royal Navy? Maybe I should tell you something about the generals who used to accompany me.
900263.mission_complete: Missions give out rewards once you complete them. Don't forget that!
900263.main: Your orders are absolute, Commander. They shall be my highest priority.|This grand old lady can run faster without a skirt. Want to race with me?|If you make fun of me one more time, you'll be eating my 15 inch shells!
900263.feeling5: Well, enough of that. I'm Warspite, the one who spites war. Hmph! However, whosoever tries to take the Commander away from me will first have to face my cannons!
900263.unlock: Greetings, I'm Warspite. I hold the record for the longest ranged hit on a moving target. Surprised? I'm smaller than you thought? Looks like we need to have a long talk...
900263.feeling4: How do I put this... I'm considered to be one of the older girls, yet my body is like this... It might be unbecoming of one my age to compete with the younger girls, but I wanted to at least be attractive to you… What is a lady meant to do…
900263.profile: Elizabeth-class fast battleship, Warspite, reporting in. I hold the record for the longest ranged hit on a moving target. I've come close to being defeated quite a few times, but I managed to cheat death every time. This must be my fate.
900263.feeling1: Would you please not act like we're close...
900263.propose: Finally the day has come! It looks like my efforts were not in vain... Let's go, Commander, I'm prepared for this. Officers, draw swords!
900263.drop_descrip: Queen Elizabeth-class battleship - Warspite, Hull Number 03!
900263.touch: Body contact...? I don't hate it...
900263.touch2: Just so you understand, I'm definitely not that sort of, erm...
900263.mission: Accept your new mission and then get ready to head out, Commander!
900263.home: Whew, not a bad fight. Let's rest for a while.
900263.win_mvp: Don't be confined by the so-called "limits". It is indeed possible to be unsinkable!
900263.expedition: Commissions? I suppose I do miss running around on errands... Let's go. We need to welcome back those hard workers!
900263.feeling3: I'm not very elegant? I'm sorry that I'm not like Hood or the others... No... I'm not talking about my body...
900263.lose: My damage control isn't functioning?! I've lost control of my steering wheel as well! Why now, at such a critical moment?!

105010.detail: At times like these, I tend to like your mindfulness...
105010.touch: Who knew you were a people person?
105010.battle: How lively! Allow me to join in the fun!
105010.feeling2: I'm quite confident in my own luck. Want to gamble a bit?
105010.main: Gambling? I'm not usually interested, but I'll give it a shot with you if you're up for it!|Commander, go do what you want while you're still young!|Bantry Bay Squadron? I just missed my chance, you see...
105010.feeling5: The idea behind priority defenses? That is to protect our most important areas... What, you want to know how important they are? W-well, if it's you...
105010.unlock: Are you the commander, young man? I'm Nevada. I'll be working with you from here on out.
105010.feeling4: If you like someone, just say it up front. What use is there to hide it? ...It's just not like you at all, Commander!
105010.feeling1: I'm a bit disappointed in you...
105010.propose: Oh you... what are you doing, getting so bold at a time like this? Have you never considered the time and place for such an important thing? Hmph. yeah yeah. I'm not saying no, so bring it.
105010.drop_descrip: Nevada-class battleship – Nevada, Hull Number BB-36!
105010.profile: Yo! I'm the big sister of the Nevada-class battleships, Nevada! I served in both the Atlantic and Pacific fleets. The President was once on board me, I've changed kidneys, carried two atomic bombs, and even cleared out an entire battlefield!
105010.touch2: Are you that interested in my 'priority defenses'?
105010.mission: As soldiers, completing missions is our divine duty.
105010.home: If you're tired, you can always rest on my shoulders. Don't be embarrassed. Come on!
105010.win_mvp: Ha, you think you can beat me with such weak firepower and defences?
105010.expedition: Commander, the commissions have returned without issue. Make sure to comlement them for their efforts!
105010.feeling3: Commander, Oklahoma told me about a nice shop around here. Wanna have a look? ... Hey, stop standing there like a pole! Let's go
105010.lose: Tsk, wait and see how I take you on next time!

105040.detail: Even me? ... Thank you very much!
105040.login: Commander, do you understand my feelings for wanting to protect my friends?
105040.battle: This time, I will protect all that I want...!
105040.hp_warning: I can't cry!... I have to cry for happy times...!
105040.feeling2: Ahh... Apologies. I was thinking about something sad again...
105040.mission_complete: Here's the list, but... Are the physical rewards really that important...?
105040.main: As long as I'm in Commander's memory, I'll never be alone|In order to not forget about them... they... have always been with me|Commander, did my facial expression bother you? I'm sorry...
105040.feeling5: I'm sorry... Ah, no, I'm just a little afraid... 'What if Commander doesn't come back after this mission?'... I can't stop my tears just thinking about it...
105040.unlock: I am the second ship of the Pennsylvania class, born during summer, Arizona. This time, I won't let that tragedy repeat itself...
105040.feeling4: I feel safe around you, Commander... I feel as if I'm not afraid to look ahead after thinking about what happened back then...
105040.feeling1: I wonder where I truly belong?
105040.propose: I won't let that day happen again' you say? ...Thank you. Those are the words that resonated with my heart the most in my life... I believe in you!
105040.drop_descrip: Pennsylvania-class Battleship –  Arizona, Hull Number BB-39!
105040.profile:
I am the second ship of the Pennsylvania class battleships, born during summer, Arizona. 
Yes... the 'Tears of Arizona' is referring to me, but it's a little sad to call them tears... you see...
105040.touch2: Uh- Let's pretend that it didn't happen, alright?
105040.mission: Commander... the... the missions. They're not done, you know?
105040.home: It's great to be back, safe and sound.
105040.win_mvp: This feels great... It would be good if the nightmares go away at this rate...
105040.expedition: The wind... A sign of the girls' return
couple_encourage: I'll work hard, big sis!
I'm going to protect everyone this time!
105040.mail: Commander, there's a mail for you. Interpersonal relationships are important.
105040.feeling3: ...Thank you for always listening to me... I've been feeling much better now...
105040.lose: No more... Just this once, please let me have it my way...

900262.detail: My standing within the Royal Family? Hmm... If I had to draw a comparison, I'd say "Knight Commander" would be the most fitting... Hahaha...
900262.touch: Why do I have a mountain of snacks before me? Isn't it obvious? One cannot move on an empty stomach.
900262.login: Commander, did you already partake of supper?
900262.battle: Let us go forth and plant our banners!
900262.feeling2: By the way, Commander, are you a good cook? Hmm? Despite my appearances, I've spent many hours honing my skills to sate my own appetite.
900262.mission_complete: Supper tastes best after the day's missions are all complete. Wouldn't you agree, Commander?
900262.feeling5: My greatest hobbies in life are food and fighting. While I am more than capable of fighting alone, dining by myself is quite difficult and lonesome. To be able to find someone who can share both of these things with me is truly a joyous thing.
900262.upgrade: Hmm... I suddenly feel like having a lavish feast.
900262.unlock: So this is my new battlefield. Ahh, how I've long awaited this... By the way, are you my commander? You are in the presence of King George V – do use me well.
900262.feeling4: Commander, so you're learning how to cook? Hmm, colour me impressed. I look forward to trying the dish that you're making for me.
900262.feeling1: I favor those of character, and those who can cook. Commander, you are neither.
900262.propose: They say that "the quickest way to one's heart is through their stomach," but you've managed to win over both at once. Commander, shall we share all our meals together from now on?
900262.drop_descrip: King George V-class battleship – King George V.
900262.skill: The glory of the sun that never sets shall not fade!
900262.touch2: Ohh? I wasn't aware that you possessed such audacity, Commander.
900262.mission: New missions, eh? It would be ideal if we got something a bit more challenging.
900262.home: Commander, did you thoroughly enjoy the battle?
900262.win_mvp: Make no mistakes. I shall ensure both victory and the safety of all my comrades.
900262.expedition: There's some commotion by the port...? Oh, it seems to just be the commission team returning.
couple_encourage: Wales, you'd better not suddenly leave me again!
York, let us shatter our enemies together.
900262.mail: A letter, huh? Now then, is this a challenge, or a love letter?
900262.feeling3: How's that, commander? Are you impressed by my cooking abilities? Here, have as much you desire. Seeing you enjoy my food pleases me.
900262.lose: Do not be demoralized. Neither victory nor defeat are decided by a single battle.

301053.detail: When I put on my headphones, the music flows and washes away everything in the world... except you...
301053.touch: Ayanami's riggings... can also become musical instruments. Commander, do you want to hear me play?
301053.login: Commander, before work starts, want to listen to music together?
301053.battle: This song... fits the battlefield well.
301053.mission_complete: I'm somewhat looking forward to today's rewards...
301053.main: Commander, Javelin asked if I could play later. Is that okay? |Commander, what kind of music do you like? I like... um, rock? |Ikazuchi said she was playing something called a "mobage." Commander, do you know what that is?
301053.unlock: Commander, want to listen to music together? Do you like... this non-combat-oriented Ayanami?
301053.drop_descrip: Commander, want to listen to music together? Do you like... this non-combat-oriented Ayanami?
301053.win_mvp: "As long as you're smiling..." What does that mean?
301053.expedition: Training and commissions... there''s no time to slack off...
